
prathamo .adhyāyaḥ|
namaḥ paramadevāya traiguṇyāvijitātmane|
sarvato yogarūpāya saṃsārābhāvahetave|| 1.1||
sthitisaṃrodhasargāṇāṃ hetave .antaḥprasāriṇe|
ṣaḍviṃśāya pradhānāya mahādevāya dhīmate|| 1.2||
prajāpatermahākṣetre gaṅgākālindisaṃgame|
prayāge parame puṇye brahmaṇo lokavartmani|| 1.3||
munayaḥ saṃśitātmānastapasā kṣīṇakalmaṣāḥ|
tīrthasaṃplavanārthāya paurṇamāsyāṃ kṛtāhnikāḥ|| 1.4||
paurāṇikam apaśyanta sūtaṃ satyaparāyaṇam|
snātvā tasmin mahātīrthe praṇāmārtham upāgatam|| 1.5||
dṛṣṭvā te sūtam āyāntam ṛṣayo hṛṣṭamānasāḥ|
āśāsyāsanasaṃveśaṃ tadyogyaṃ samakalpayan|| 1.6||
sa praṇamya ca tān sarvān sūtastān munipuṃgavān|
pradattam āsanaṃ bheje sarvadharmasamanvitaḥ|| 1.7||
tam āsīnam apṛcchanta munayastapasaidhitāḥ|
brahmasattre purā sādho naimiśāraṇyavāsinām|| 1.8||
kathitaṃ bhāratākhyānaṃ purāṇaṃ ca paraṃ tvayā|
tena naḥ pratibhāsi tvaṃ sākṣāt satyavatīsutaḥ|| 1.9||
sarvāgamaparārthajñaḥ satyadharmaparāyaṇaḥ|
dvijapūjārato nityaṃ tena pṛcchāṃ tvam arhasi|| 1.10||
bhāratākhyānasadṛśaṃ purāṇādyadviśiṣyate|
tat tvā pṛcchāma vai janma kārttikeyasya dhīmataḥ|| 1.11||
ime hi munayaḥ sarve tvadupāstiparāyaṇāḥ|
skandasaṃbhavaśuśrūṣāsaṃjātautsukyamānasāḥ|| 1.12||
evamuktastadā sūtaḥ saṃsiddhairmunipuṃgavaiḥ|
provācedaṃ munīn sarvān vaco bhūtārthavācakam|| 1.13||
śṛṇudhvaṃ munayaḥ sarve kārttikeyasya sambhavam|
brahmaṇyatvaṃ samāhātmyaṃ vīryaṃ ca tridaśādhikam|| 1.14||
mumukṣayā paraṃ sthānaṃ yāte śukamahātmani|
sutaśokābhisaṃtapto vyāsastryambakam aikṣata|| 1.15||
dṛṣṭvaiva sa maheśānaṃ vyāso 'abhūdvigatavyathaḥ|
vicaran sa tadā lokān muniḥ satyavatīsutaḥ|| 1.16||
meruśṛṅge 'atha dadṛśe brahmaṇaḥ sutam agrajam|
sanatkumāraṃ varadaṃ yogaiśvaryasamanvitam|| 1.17||
vimāne ravisaṃkāśe tiṣṭhantam analaprabham|
munibhiryogasaṃsiddhaistapoyuktairmahātmabhiḥ|| 1.18||
vedavedāṅgatattvajñaiḥ sarvadharmāgamānvitaiḥ|
sakalāvāptavidyaistu caturvaktram ivāvṛtam|| 1.19||
dṛṣṭvā taṃ sumahātmānaṃ vyāso munim athāsthitam|
vavande parayā bhaktyā sākṣādiva pitāmaham|| 1.20||
brahmasūnuratha vyāsaṃ samāyātaṃ mahaujasam|
pariṣvajya paraṃ premṇā provāca vacanaṃ śubham|| 1.21||
diṣṭyā tvam asi dharmajña prasādāt pārameśvarāt|
apetaśokaḥ samprāptaḥ pṛcchasva pravadāmyaham|| 1.22||
śrutvātha vacanaṃ sūnorbrahmaṇo munipuṃgavaḥ|
idam āha vaco viprāściraṃ yaddhṛdaye sthitam|| 1.23||
kumārasya kathaṃ janma kārttikeyasya dhīmataḥ|
kiṃnimittaṃ kuto vāsya icchāmyetaddhi veditum|| 1.24||
kathaṃ rudrasutaścāsau vahnigaṅgāsutaḥ katham|
umāyāstanayaścaiva svāhāyāśca kathaṃ punaḥ |
suparṇyāścātha mātR̥ṇāṃ kṛttikānāṃ kathaṃ ca saḥ|| 1.25||
kaścāsau pūrvam utpannaḥ kiṃtapāḥ kaśca vikramaḥ|
bhūtasaṃmohanaṃ hyetat kathayasva yathātatham|| 1.26||
sūta uvāca|
evaṃ sa pṛṣṭastejasvī brahmaṇaḥ putrasattamaḥ|
uvāca sarvaṃ sarvajño vyāsāyākliṣṭakāriṇe|
tacchṛṇudhvaṃ yathātattvaṃ kīrtyamānaṃ mayānaghāḥ|| 1.27||
iti skandapurāṇe prathamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 1.1||

dvitīyo .adhyāyaḥ
sanatkumāra uvāca|
prapadye devam īśānaṃ sarvajñam aparājitam|
mahādevaṃ mahātmānaṃ viśvasya jagataḥ patim|| 2.1||
śaktirapratighā yasya aiśvaryaṃ caiva sarvaśaḥ|
svāmitvaṃ ca vibhutvaṃ ca svakṛtāni pracakṣate|| 2.2||
tasmai devāya somāya praṇamya prayataḥ śuciḥ|
purāṇākhyānajijñāsorvakṣye skandodbhavaṃ śubham|| 2.3||
dehāvatāro devasya rudrasya paramātmanaḥ|
prājāpatyābhiṣekaśca haraṇaṃ śirasastathā|| 2.4||
darśanaṃ ṣaṭkulīyānāṃ cakrasya ca visarjanam|
naimiśasyodbhavaścaiva sattrasya ca samāpanam|| 2.5||
brahmaṇaścāgamastatra tapasaścaraṇaṃ tathā|
śarvasya darśanaṃ caiva devyāścaiva samudbhavaḥ|| 2.6||
satyā vivādaśca tathā dakṣaśāpastathaiva ca|
menāyāṃ ca yathotpattiryathā devyāḥ svayaṃvaram|| 2.7||
devānāṃ varadānaṃ ca vasiṣṭhasya ca dhīmataḥ|
parāśarasya cotpattirvyāsasya ca mahātmanaḥ|| 2.8||
vasiṣṭhakauśikābhyāṃ ca vairodbhavasamāpanam|
vārāṇasyāśca śūnyatvaṃ kṣetramāhātmyavarṇanam|| 2.9||
rudrasya cātra sāṃnidhyaṃ nandinaścāpyanugrahaḥ|
gaṇānāṃ darśanaṃ caiva kathanaṃ cāpyaśeṣataḥ|| 2.10||
kālīvyāharaṇaṃ caiva tapaścaraṇam eva ca|
somanandisamākhyānaṃ varadānaṃ tathaiva ca|| 2.11||
gaurītvaṃ putralambhaśca devyā utpattireva ca|
kauśikyā bhūtamātṛtvaṃ siṃhāśca rathinastathā|| 2.12||
gauryāśca nilayo vindhye vindhyasūryasamāgamaḥ|
agastyasya ca māhātmyaṃ vadhaḥ sundanisundayoḥ|| 2.13||
nisumbhasumbhaniryāṇaṃ mahiṣasya vadhastathā|
abhiṣekaśca kauśikyā varadānam athāpi ca|| 2.14||
andhakasya tathotpattiḥ pṛthivyāścaiva bandhanam|
hiraṇyākṣavadhaścaiva hiraṇyakaśipostathā|| 2.15||
balisaṃyamanaṃ caiva devyāḥ samaya eva ca|
devānāṃ gamanaṃ caiva agnerdūtatvam eva ca|| 2.16||
devānāṃ varadānaṃ ca śukrasya ca visarjanam|
sutasya ca tathotpattirdevyāścāndhakadarśanam|| 2.17||
śailādidaityasaṃmardo devyāśca śatarūpatā|
āryāvarapradānaṃ ca śailādistava eva ca|| 2.18||
devasyāgamanaṃ caiva vṛttasya kathanaṃ tathā|
pativratāyāścākhyānaṃ guruśuśrūṣaṇasya ca|| 2.19||
ākhyānaṃ pañcacūḍāyāstejasaścāpyadhṛṣyatā|
dūtasyāgamanaṃ caiva saṃvādo 'atha visarjanam|| 2.20||
andhakāsurasaṃvādo mandarāgamanaṃ tathā|
gaṇānām āgamaścaiva saṃkhyānaśravaṇaṃ tathā|| 2.21||
nigrahaścāndhakasyātha yuddhena mahatā tathā|
śarīrārdhapradānaṃ ca aśokasutasaṃgrahaḥ|| 2.22||
bhasmasomodbhavaścaiva śmaśānavasatistathā|
rudrasya nīlakaṇṭhatvaṃ tathāyatanavarṇanam|| 2.23||
utpattiryakṣarājasya kuberasya ca dhīmataḥ|
nigraho bhujagendrāṇāṃ śikharasya ca pātanam|| 2.24||
trailokyasya saśakrasya vaśīkaraṇam eva ca|
devasenāpradānaṃ ca senāpatyābhiṣecanam|| 2.25||
nāradasyāgamaścaiva tārakapreṣitasya ha|
vadhaśca tārakasyogro yātrā bhadravaṭasya ca|| 2.26||
mahiṣasya vadhaścaiva krauñcasya ca nibarhaṇam|
śakteruddharaṇaṃ caiva tārakasya vadhaḥ śubhaḥ|| 2.27||
devāsurabhayotpattistraipuraṃ yuddham eva ca|
prahlādavigrahaścaiva kṛtaghnākhyānam eva ca|
mahābhāgyaṃ brāhmaṇānāṃ vistareṇa prakīrtyate|| 2.28||
etajjñātvā yathāvaddhi kumārānucaro bhavet|
balavān matisampannaḥ putraṃ cāpnoti saṃmatam|| 2.29||
iti skandapurāṇe dvitīyo .adhyāyaḥ|| 2.2||

tṛtīyo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇuṣvemāṃ kathāṃ divyāṃ sarvapāpapraṇāśanīm|
kathyamānāṃ mayā citrāṃ bahvarthāṃ śrutisaṃmitām|
yāṃ śrutvā pāpakarmāpi gacchecca paramāṃ gatim|| 3.1||
na nāstikāśraddadhāne śaṭhe cāpi kathaṃcana|
imāṃ kathām anubrūyāt tathā cāsūyake nare|| 3.2||
idaṃ putrāya śiṣyāya dhārmikāyānasūyave|
kathanīyaṃ mahābrahman devabhaktāya vā bhavet|
kumārabhaktāya tathā śraddadhānāya caiva hi|| 3.3||
purā brahmā prajādhyakṣaḥ aṇḍe 'asmin samprasūyate|
so 'ajñānāt pitaraṃ brahmā na veda tamasāvṛtaḥ|| 3.4||
aham eka iti jñātvā sarvā/llokānavaikṣata|
na cāpaśyata tatrānyaṃ tapoyogabalānvitaḥ|| 3.5||
putra putreti cāpyukto brahmā śarveṇa dhīmatā|
praṇataḥ prāñjalirbhūtvā tam eva śaraṇaṃ gataḥ|| 3.6||
sa dattvā brahmaṇe śambhuḥ sraṣṭṛtvaṃ jñānasaṃhitam|
vibhutvaṃ caiva lokānām antardhe parameśvaraḥ|| 3.7||
tad eṣopaniṣat proktā mayā vyāsa sanātanā|
yāṃ śrutvā yogino dhyānāt prapadyante maheśvaram|| 3.8||
brahmaṃ ca yo vidadhe putram agre jñānaṃ ca yaḥ prahiṇoti sma tasmai|
tam ātmasthaṃ ye 'anupaśyanti dhīrāsteṣāṃ śāntiḥ śāśvatī netareṣām|| 3.9||
sa vyāsa pitaraṃ dṛṣṭvā svadīptyā parayā yutam|
putrakāmaḥ prajāhetostapastīvraṃ cakāra ha|| 3.10||
mahatā yogatapasā yuktasya sumahātmanaḥ|
acireṇaiva kālena pitā sampratutoṣa ha|| 3.11||
darśanaṃ cāgamat tasya varado 'asmītyuvāca ha|
sa tuṣṭāva nato bhūtvā kṛtvā śirasi cāñjalim|| 3.12||
namaḥ paramadevāya devānām api vedhase|
sraṣṭre vai lokatantrāya brahmaṇaḥ pataye namaḥ|| 3.13||
ekasmai śaktiyuktāya aśaktirahitāya ca|
anantāyāprameyāya indriyāviṣayāya ca|| 3.14||
vyāpine vyāptapūrvāya adhiṣṭhātre pracodine|
kṛtapracetanāyaiva tattvavinyāsakāriṇe|| 3.15||
pradhānacodakāyaiva guṇināṃ śāntidāya ca|
dṛṣṭidāya ca sarveṣāṃ svayaṃ vai darśanāya ca|| 3.16||
viṣayagrāhiṇe caiva niyamasya ca kāriṇe|
manasaḥ karaṇānāṃ ca tatraiva niyamasya ca|| 3.17||
bhūtānāṃ guṇakartre ca śaktidāya tathaiva ca|
kartre hyaṇḍasya mahyaṃ ca acintyāyāgrajāya ca|
aprameya pitarnityaṃ prīto no diśa śakvarīm|| 3.18||
tasyaivaṃ stuvato vyāsa devadevo maheśvaraḥ|
tuṣṭo 'abravīt svayaṃ putraṃ brahmāṇaṃ praṇataṃ tathā|| 3.19||
yasmāt te viditaṃ vatsa sūkṣmam etanmahādyute|
tasmādbrahmeti lokeṣu nāmnā khyātiṃ gamiṣyasi|| 3.20||
yasmāccāhaṃ pitetyuktastvayā buddhimatāṃ vara|
tasmāt pitāmahatvaṃ te loke khyātiṃ gamiṣyati|| 3.21||
prajārthaṃ yacca te taptaṃ tapa ugraṃ suduścaram|
tasmāt prajāpatitvaṃ te dadāni prayatātmane|| 3.22||
evam uktvā sa deveśo mūrtimatyo 'asṛjat striyaḥ|
yāstāḥ prakṛtayastvaṣṭau viśeṣāścendriyaiḥ saha|
bhāvāśca sarve te devam upatasthuḥ svarūpiṇaḥ|| 3.23||
tānuvāca tato devaḥ patiryuktaḥ svatejasā|
etam adyābhiṣekeṇa sampādayata mā ciram|| 3.24||
tābhiḥ svaṃ svaṃ samādāya bhāvaṃ divyam atarkitam|
abhiṣikto babhūveti prajāpatiratidyutiḥ|| 3.25||
tatraivaṃ yoginaḥ sūkṣmaṃ dṛṣṭvā divyena cakṣuṣā|
purāṇaṃ yogatattvajñā gāyanti triguṇānvitam|| 3.26||
rudraḥ sraṣṭā hi sarveṣāṃ bhūtānāṃ tava ca prabho|
asmābhiśca bhavān sārdhaṃ jagataḥ sampravartakaḥ|| 3.27||
sa devastoṣitaḥ samyak paramaiśvaryayogadhṛk|
brahmāṇam agrajaṃ putraṃ prājāpatye 'abhyaṣecayat|| 3.28||
yaḥ kṛtvā bahuvidhamārgayogayuktaṃ tattvākhyaṃ jagadidam ādarādyuyoja|
sarveṣāṃ manasi sadāvatiṣṭhamāno jānānaḥ śubham aśubhaṃ ca bhūtanāthaḥ|
taṃ devaṃ pramathapatiṃ praṇamya bhaktyā nityaṃ vai śaraṇam upaimi sūkṣmasūkṣmam|| 3.30||
iti skandapurāṇe tṛtīyo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 3.3||

caturtho .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
prājāpatyaṃ tato labdhvā prajāḥ sraṣṭuṃ pracakrame|
prajāstāḥ sṛjyamānāśca na vivardhanti tasya ha|| 4.1||
sa kurvāṇastathā sṛṣṭiṃ śaktihīnaḥ pitāmahaḥ|
sṛṣṭyarthaṃ bhūya evātha tapaścartuṃ pracakrame|| 4.2||
sṛṣṭihetostapastasya jñātvā tribhuvaneśvaraḥ|
tejasā jagadāviśya ājagāma tadantikam|
sraṣṭā tasya jagannātho 'adarśayat svatanau jagat|| 4.3||
svayam āgatya deveśo mahābhūtapatirharaḥ|
vyāpyeva hi jagat kṛtsnaṃ parameṇa svatejasā|
śambhuḥ prāha varaṃ vatsa yācasveti pitāmaham|| 4.4||
taṃ brahmā lokasṛṣṭyarthaṃ putrastvaṃ manasābravīt|
sa jñātvā tasya saṃkalpaṃ brahmaṇaḥ parameśvaraḥ|
mūḍho 'ayam iti saṃcintya provāca varadaḥ svayam|| 4.5||
āgataṃ pitaraṃ mā tvaṃ yasmāt putraṃ samīhase|
manmūrtistanayastasmādbhaviṣyati mamājñayā|| 4.6||
sa ca te putratāṃ yātvā madīyo gaṇanāyakaḥ|
rudro vigrahavān bhūtvā mūḍha tvāṃ vinayiṣyati|| 4.7||
sarvavidyādhipatyaṃ ca yogānāṃ caiva sarvaśaḥ|
balasyādhipatitvaṃ ca astrāṇāṃ ca prayoktṛtā|| 4.8||
mayā dattāni tasyāśu upasthāsyanti sarvaśaḥ|
dhanuḥ pinākaṃ śūlaṃ ca khaḍgaṃ paraśureva ca|| 4.9||
kamaṇḍalustathā daṇḍaḥ astraṃ pāśupataṃ tathā|
saṃvartakāśaniścaiva cakraṃ ca pratisargikam|
evaṃ sarvarddhisampannaḥ sutaste sa bhaviṣyati|| 4.10||
evam uktvā gate tasminnantardhānaṃ mahātmani|
brahmā cakre tadā ceṣṭiṃ putrakāmaḥ prajāpatiḥ|| 4.11||
sa juhvañchramasaṃyuktaḥ pratighātasamanvitaḥ|
samidyuktena hastena lalāṭaṃ pramamārja ha|| 4.12||
taddhi māheśvaraṃ tejaḥ saṃdhitaṃ brahmaṇi srutam|
preritaṃ devadevena nipapāta havirbhuji|| 4.14||
kṣaṇe tasmin maheśena smṛtvā taṃ varam uttamam|
preṣito gaṇapo rudraḥ sadya evābhavat tadā|| 4.15||
tacca saṃsvedajaṃ tejaḥ pūrvaṃ jvalanayojitam|
bhūtvā lohitam āśveva punarnīlam abhūt tadā|| 4.16||
nīlalohita ityeva tenāsāvabhavat prabhuḥ|
tryakṣo daśabhujaḥ śrīmān brahmāṇaṃ chādayanniva|| 4.17||
śarvādyairnāmabhirbrahmā tanūbhiśca jalādibhiḥ|
stutvā taṃ sarvagaṃ devaṃ nīlalohitam avyayam|| 4.18||
jñātvā sarvasṛjaṃ paścānmahābhūtapratiṣṭhitam|
asṛjadvividhāstvanyāḥ prajāḥ sa jagati prabhuḥ|| 4.19||
so 'api yogaṃ samāsthāya aiśvaryeṇa samanvitaḥ|
lokān sarvān samāviśya dhārayāmāsa sarvadā|| 4.20||
brahmaṇo 'api tataḥ putrā dakṣadharmādayaḥ śubhāḥ|
asṛjanta prajāḥ sarvā devamānuṣasaṃkulāḥ|| 4.21||
atha kālena mahatā kalpe 'atīte punaḥ punaḥ|
prajā dhārayato yogādasmin kalpa upasthite|| 4.22||
pratiṣṭhitāyāṃ vārttāyāṃ pravṛtte vṛṣṭisarjane|
prajāsu ca vivṛddhāsu prayāge yajataśca ha|| 4.23||
brahmaṇaḥ ṣaṭkulīyāste ṛṣayaḥ saṃśitavratāḥ|
marīcayo 'atrayaścaiva vasiṣṭhāḥ kratavastathā|| 4.24||
bhṛgavo 'aṅgirasaścaiva tapasā dagdhakilbiṣāḥ|
ūcurbrahmāṇam abhyetya sahitāḥ karmaṇo 'antare|| 4.25||
bhagavannandhakāreṇa mahatā smaḥ samāvṛtāḥ|
khinnā vivadamānāśca na ca paśyāma yat param|| 4.26||
etaṃ naḥ saṃśayaṃ deva ciraṃ hṛdi samāsthitam|
tvaṃ hi vettha yathātattvaṃ kāraṇaṃ paramaṃ hi naḥ|| 4.27||
kiṃ paraṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ balīyaścāpi sarvataḥ|
kena cādhiṣṭhitaṃ viśvaṃ ko nityaḥ kaśca śāśvataḥ|| 4.28||
kaḥ sraṣṭā sarvabhūtānāṃ prakṛteśca pravartakaḥ|
ko 'asmān sarveṣu kāryeṣu prayunakti mahāmanāḥ|| 4.29||
kasya bhūtāni vaśyāni kaḥ sarvaviniyojakaḥ|
kathaṃ paśyema taṃ caiva etannaḥ śaṃsa sarvaśaḥ|| 4.30||
evamuktastato brahmā sarveṣām eva saṃnidhau|
devānāṃ ca ṛṣīṇāṃ ca gandharvoragarakṣasām|| 4.31||
yakṣāṇām asurāṇāṃ ca ye ca kutra pravartakāḥ|
pakṣiṇāṃ sapiśācānāṃ ye cānye tatsamīpagāḥ|
utthāya prāñjaliḥ prāha rudreti triḥ plutaṃ vacaḥ|| 4.32||
sa cāpi tapasā śakyo draṣṭuṃ nānyena kenacit|
sa sraṣṭā sarvabhūtānāṃ balavāṃstanmayaṃ jagat |
tasya vaśyāni bhūtāni tenedaṃ dhāryate jagat|| 4.33||
tataste sarvalokeśā namaścakrurmahātmane|| 4.34||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ|
kiṃ tanmahat tapo deva yena dṛśyeta sa prabhuḥ|
tanno vadasva deveśa $\uw{$varadaṃ}${3.2}$ cābhidhatsva naḥ|| 4.35||
pitāmaha uvāca|
sattraṃ mahat samāsadhvaṃ vāṅmanodoṣavarjitāḥ|
deśaṃ ca vaḥ pravakṣyāmi yasmin deśe cariṣyatha|| 4.36||
tato manomayaṃ cakraṃ sa sṛṣṭvā tānuvāca ha|
kṣiptam etanmayā cakram anuvrajata mā ciram|| 4.37||
yatrāsya nemiḥ śīryeta sa deśastapasaḥ śubhaḥ|
tato mumoca taccakraṃ te ca tat samanuvrajan|| 4.38||
tasya vai vrajataḥ kṣipraṃ yatra nemiraśīryata|
naimiśaṃ tat smṛtaṃ nāmnā puṇyaṃ sarvatra pūjitam|| 4.39||
tat pūjitaṃ devamanuṣyasiddhai rakṣobhirugrairuragaiśca divyaiḥ|
yakṣaiḥ sagandharvapiśācasaṃghaiḥ sarvāpsarobhiśca diteḥ sutaiśca|| 4.40||
vipraiśca dāntaiḥ śamayogayuktaistīrthaiśca sarvairapi cāvanīdhraiḥ|
gandharvavidyādharacāraṇaiśca sādhyaiśca viśvaiḥ pitṛbhiḥ stutaṃ ca|| 4.41||
iti skandapurāṇe caturtho .adhyāyaḥ|| 4.4||

pañcamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tannaimiśaṃ samāsādya ṛṣayo dīptatejasaḥ|
divyaṃ sattraṃ samāsanta mahadvarṣasahasrikam|| 5.1||
ekāgramanasaḥ sarve nirmamā hyanahaṃkṛtāḥ|
dhyāyanto nityam īśeśaṃ sadāratanayāgnayaḥ|| 5.2||
tanniṣṭhāstatparāḥ sarve tadyuktāstadapāśrayāḥ|
sarvakriyāḥ prakurvāṇāstam eva manasā gatāḥ|| 5.3||
teṣāṃ taṃ bhāvam ālakṣya mātariśvā mahātapāḥ|
sarvaprāṇicaraḥ śrīmān sarvabhūtapravartakaḥ|
dadau sa rūpī bhagavān darśanaṃ sattriṇāṃ śubhaḥ|| 5.4||
taṃ te dṛṣṭvārcayitvā ca mātariśvānam avyayam|
āsīnam āsane puṇye ṛṣayaḥ saṃśitavratāḥ|
papracchurudbhavaṃ kṛtsnaṃ jagataḥ pralayaṃ tathā|| 5.5||
sthitiṃ ca kṛtsnāṃ vaṃśāṃśca yugamanvantarāṇi ca|
vaṃśānucaritaṃ kṛtsnaṃ divyamānaṃ tathaiva ca|| 5.6||
aṣṭānāṃ devayonīnām utpattiṃ pralayaṃ tathā|
pitṛsargaṃ tathāśeṣaṃ brahmaṇo mānam eva ca|| 5.7||
candrādityagatiṃ sarvāṃ tārāgrahagatiṃ tathā|
sthitiṃ sarveśvarāṇāṃ ca dvīpadharmam aśeṣataḥ|
varṇāśramavyavasthānaṃ yajñānāṃ ca pravartanam|| 5.8||
etat sarvam aśeṣeṇa kathayāmāsa sa prabhuḥ|
divyaṃ varṣasahasraṃ ca teṣāṃ tadabhiyāt tathā|| 5.9||
atha divyena rūpeṇa sāmavāgdiṅnirīkṣaṇā|
yajurghrāṇātharvaśirāḥ śabdajihvā śubhā satī|| 5.10||
nyāyaśrotrā niruktatvagṛkpādapadagāminī|
kālabāhūrvarṣakarā divasāṅgulidhāriṇī|| 5.11||
kalādibhiḥ parvabhiśca māsaiḥ kararuhaistathā|
kalpasādhāraṇā divyā śikṣāvidyonnatastanī|| 5.12||
chandovicitimadhyā ca mīmāṃsānābhireva ca|
purāṇavistīrṇakaṭirdharmaśāstramanorathā|| 5.13||
āśramorūrvarṇajānuryajñagulphā phalāṅguliḥ|
lokavedaśarīrā ca romabhiśchāndasaiḥ śubhaiḥ|| 5.14||
śraddhāśubhācāravastrā yogadharmābhibhāṣiṇī|
vedīmadhyādviniḥsṛtya pravṛttā paramāmbhasā|| 5.15||
tasyānte 'avabhṛthe plutya vāyunā saha saṃgatāḥ|
tām apṛcchanta kā nveṣā vāyuṃ devaṃ mahādhiyam|| 5.16||
uvāca sa mahātejā ṛṣīn dharmānubhāvitān|
śuddhāḥ stha tapasā sarve mahān dharmaśca vaḥ kṛtaḥ|| 5.17||
yasmādiyaṃ nadī puṇyā brahmalokādihāgatā|
iyaṃ sarasvatī nāma brahmalokavibhūṣaṇā|| 5.18||
prathamaṃ martyaloke 'asmin yuṣmatsiddhyartham āgatā|
nāsyāḥ puṇyatamā kācit triṣu lokeṣu vidyate|| 5.19||
vāyuruvāca|
atra vo vartayiṣyāmi itihāsaṃ purātanam|
brahmaṇaścaiva saṃvādaṃ purā yajñasya caiva ha|| 5.21||
yajñairiṣṭvā purā devo brahmā dīptena tejasā|
asṛjat sarvabhūtāni sthāvarāṇi carāṇi ca|| 5.22||
sa dṛṣṭvā dīptimān devo dīptyā paramayā yutaḥ|
avekṣamāṇaḥ svā/llokāṃścaturbhirmukhapaṅkajaiḥ|| 5.23||
devādīn manuṣyādīṃśca dṛṣṭvā dṛṣṭvā mahāmanāḥ|
amanyata na me 'anyo 'asti samo loke na cādhikaḥ|| 5.24||
ahaṃ sraṣṭā hi bhūtānāṃ nānyaḥ kaścana vidyate|
niyantā lokakartā ca na mayāsti samaḥ kvacit|| 5.26||
tasyaivaṃ manyamānasya yajña āgānmahāmanāḥ|
uvāca cainaṃ dīptātmā maivaṃ maṃsthā mahāmate|
ayaṃ hi tava saṃmoho vināśāya bhaviṣyati|| 5.27||
na yuktam īdṛśaṃ te 'adya sattvasthasyātmayoninaḥ|
sraṣṭā tvaṃ caiva nānyo 'asti tathāpi na yaśaskaram|| 5.28||
ahaṃ kartā hi bhūtānāṃ bhuvanasya tathaiva ca|
karomi na ca saṃmohaṃ yathā tvaṃ deva katthase|| 5.29||
tam uvāca tadā brahmā na tvaṃ dhārayitā vibho|
aham eva hi bhūtānāṃ dhartā bhartā tathaiva ca|
mayā sṛṣṭāni bhūtāni tvam evātra vimuhyase|| 5.30||
athāgāt tatra saṃvigno vedaḥ paramadīptimān|
uvāca caiva tau vedo naitadevam iti prabhuḥ|| 5.31||
ahaṃ śreṣṭho mahābhāgau na vadāmyanṛtaṃ kvacit|
śṛṇudhvaṃ mama yaḥ kartā bhūtānāṃ yuvayośca ha|| 5.32||
parameśo mahādevo rudraḥ sarvagataḥ prabhuḥ|
yenāhaṃ tava dattaśca kṛtastvaṃ ca prajāpatiḥ|| 5.33||
yajño 'ayaṃ yatprasūtiśca aṇḍaṃ yatrāsti saṃsthitam|
sarvaṃ tasmāt prasūtaṃ vai nānyaḥ kartāsti naḥ kvacit|| 5.34||
tam evaṃvādinaṃ devo brahmā vedam abhāṣata|
ahaṃ śrutīnāṃ sarvāsāṃ netā sraṣṭā tathaiva ca|| 5.35||
matprasādāddhi vedastvaṃ yajñaścāyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ|
mūḍhau yuvām adharmo vā bhavadbhyām anyathā kṛtaḥ|
prāyaścittaṃ caradhvaṃ vaḥ kilbiṣānmokṣyathastataḥ|| 5.36||
evam ukte tadā tena mahāñchabdo babhūva ha|
ādityamaṇḍalākāram adṛśyata ca maṇḍalam|
mahacchabdena mahatā upariṣṭādviyatsthitam|| 5.37||
sa cāpi tasmādvibhraṣṭo bhūtalaṃ samupāśritaḥ|
himavatkuñjam āsādya nānāvihaganāditam|
vyomagaśca ciraṃ bhūtvā bhūmigaḥ sambabhūva ha|| 5.38||
tato brahmā diśaḥ sarvā nirīkṣya mukhapaṅkajaiḥ|
caturbhirna viyatsthaṃ tam apaśyat sa pitāmahaḥ|| 5.39||
sa mukhaṃ pañcamaṃ dīptam asṛjanmūrdhni saṃsthitam|
tenāpaśyadviyatsthaṃ taṃ sūryāyutasamaprabham|
ādityamaṇḍalākāraṃ śabdavadghoradarśanam|| 5.40||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā pañcamaṃ tasya śiro vai krodhajaṃ mahat|
saṃvartakāgnisadṛśaṃ grasiṣyat tam avardhata|| 5.41||
vardhamānaṃ tadā tat tu vaḍavāmukhasaṃnibham|
dīptimacchabdavaccaiva devo 'asau dīptamaṇḍalaḥ|| 5.42||
hastāṅguṣṭhanakhenāśu vāmenāvajñayaiva hi|
cakarta tanmahadghoraṃ brahmaṇaḥ pañcamaṃ śiraḥ|| 5.43||
dīptikṛttaśirāḥ so 'atha duḥkhenosreṇa cārditaḥ|
papāta mūḍhacetā vai yogadharmavivarjitaḥ|| 5.44||
tataḥ suptotthita iva saṃjñāṃ labdhvā mahātapāḥ|
maṇḍalasthaṃ mahādevam astauṣīddīnayā girā|| 5.45||
brahmovāca|
namaḥ sahasranetrāya śatanetrāya vai namaḥ|
namo vivṛtavaktrāya śatavaktrāya vai namaḥ|| 5.46||
namaḥ sahasravaktrāya sarvavaktrāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ sahasrapādāya sarvapādāya vai namaḥ|| 5.47||
sahasrapāṇaye caiva sarvataḥpāṇaye namaḥ|
namaḥ sarvasya sraṣṭre ca draṣṭre sarvasya te namaḥ|| 5.48||
ādityavarṇāya namaḥ śirasaśchedanāya ca|
sṛṣṭipralayakartre ca sthitikartre tathā namaḥ|| 5.49||
namaḥ sahasraliṅgāya sahasracaraṇāya ca|
saṃhāraliṅgine caiva jalaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 5.50||
antaścarāya sarvāya prakṛteḥ preraṇāya ca|
vyāpine sarvasattvānāṃ puruṣaprerakāya ca|| 5.51||
indriyārthaviśeṣāya tathā niyamakāriṇe|
bhūtabhavyāya śarvāya nityaṃ sattvavadāya ca|| 5.52||
tvam eva sraṣṭā lokānāṃ mantā dātā tathā vibho|
śaraṇāgatāya dāntāya prasādaṃ kartum arhasi|| 5.53||
tasyaivaṃ stuvataḥ samyag bhāvena parameṇa ha|
sa tasmai devadeveśo divyaṃ cakṣuradāt tadā|| 5.54||
cakṣuṣā tena sa tadā brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
vimāne sūryasaṃkāśe tejorāśim apaśyata|| 5.55||
tasya madhyāt tato vācaṃ mahatīṃ samaśṛṇvata|
gambhīrāṃ madhurāṃ yuktām atha sampannalakṣaṇām|
viśadāṃ putra putreti pūrvaṃ devena coditām|| 5.56||
saṃsvedāt putra utpanno yat tubhyaṃ nīlalohitaḥ|
yacca pūrvaṃ mayā proktastvaṃ tadā sutamārgaṇe|| 5.57||
madīyo gaṇapo yaste manmūrtiśca bhaviṣyati|
sa prāpya paramaṃ jñānaṃ mūḍha tvā vinayiṣyati|| 5.58||
tasyeyaṃ phalaniṣpattiḥ śirasaśchedanaṃ tava|
mayaiva kāritā tena nirvṛtaścādhunā bhava|| 5.59||
tasya caivotpathasthasya yajñasya tu mahāmate|
śiraśchetsyatyasāveva kasmiṃścit kāraṇāntare|
stavenānena tuṣṭo 'asmi kiṃ dadāni ca te 'anagha|| 5.60||
vāyuruvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān hṛṣṭaḥ praṇamya śubhayā girā|
uvāca prāñjalirbhūtvā lakṣyālakṣyaṃ tam īśvaram|| 5.61||
bhagavan naiva me duḥkhaṃ darśanāt te prabādhate|
icchāmi śiraso hyasya dhāraṇaṃ sarvadā tvayā|
nanu smareyam etacca śirasaśchedanaṃ vibho|| 5.62||
bhūyaścādharmakāryebhyastvayaivecche nivāraṇam|
tathā ca kṛtyam uddiśya paśyeyaṃ tvā yathāsukham|| 5.63||
vijñaptiṃ brahmaṇaḥ śrutvā provāca bhuvaneśvaraḥ|
sa eva sutasaṃjñaste manmūrtirnīlalohitaḥ|
śiraśchetsyati yajñasya bibhartsyati śiraśca te|| 5.64||
ityuktvā devadeveśastatraivāntaradhīyata|
gate tasmin mahādeve brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
sayajñaḥ sahavedaśca svaṃ lokaṃ pratyapadyata|| 5.65||
vāyuruvāca|
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyānmartyo guhyaṃ vedārthasaṃmitam|
sa dehabhedam āsādya sāyujyaṃ brahmaṇo vrajet|| 5.66||
yaścemaṃ paṭhate nityaṃ brāhmaṇānāṃ samīpataḥ|
sa sarvapāpanirmukto rudraloke mahīyate|| 5.67||
nāputraśiṣyayogibhya idam ākhyānam aiśvaram|
ākhyeyaṃ nāpi cājñāya na śaṭhāya na mānine|| 5.68||
idaṃ mahaddivyam adharmaśāsanaṃ paṭhet sadā brāhmaṇavaidyasaṃsadi|
kṛtāvakāśo bhavatīha mānavaḥ śarīrabhede praviśet pitāmaham|| 5.69||
iti skandapurāṇe pañcamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 5.5||

ṣaṣṭho .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaḥ kapardī nīlalohitaḥ|
ājñayā parameśasya jagrāha brahmaṇaḥ śiraḥ|| 6.1||
tadgṛhītvā śiro dīptaṃ rūpaṃ vikṛtam āsthitaḥ|
yogakrīḍāṃ samāsthāya bhaikṣāya pracacāra ha|| 6.2||
sa devaveśmani tadā bhikṣārtham agamaddvijāḥ|
na cāsya kaścit tāṃ bhikṣām anurūpām adādvibhoḥ|| 6.3||
abhyagāt saṃkrameṇaiva veśma viṣṇormahātmanaḥ|
tasyātiṣṭhata sa dvāri bhikṣām uccārayañchubhām|| 6.4||
sa dṛṣṭvā tadupasthaṃ tu viṣṇurvai yogacakṣuṣā|
śirāṃ lalāṭāt sambhidya raktadhārām apātayat|
papāta sā ca vistīrṇā yojanārdhaśataṃ tadā|| 6.5||
tayā patantyā viprendrā bahūnyabdāni dhārayā|
pitāmahakapālasya nārdham apyabhipūritam|
tam uvāca tato devaḥ prahasya vacanaṃ śubham|| 6.6||
sakṛt kanyāḥ pradīyante sakṛdagniśca jāyate|
sakṛdrājāno bruvate sakṛdbhikṣā pradīyate|| 6.7||
tuṣṭo 'asmi tava dānena yuktenānena mānada|
varaṃ varaya bhadraṃ te varado 'asmi tavādya vai|| 6.8||
viṣṇuruvāca|
eṣa eva varaḥ ślāghyo yadahaṃ devatādhipam|
paśyāmi śaṃkaraṃ devam ugraṃ śarvaṃ kapardinam|| 6.9||
devaśchāyāṃ tato vīkṣya kapālasthe tadā rase|
sasarja puruṣaṃ dīptaṃ viṣṇoḥ sadṛśam ūrjitam|| 6.10||
tam āhāthākṣayaścāsi ajarāmara eva ca|
yuddheṣu cāpratidvandvī sakhā viṣṇoranuttamaḥ|
devakāryakaraḥ śrīmān sahānena carasva ca|| 6.11||
nārāsu janma yasmāt te viṣṇudehodbhavāsu ca|
narastasmāddhi nāmnā tvaṃ priyaścāsya bhaviṣyasi|| 6.12||
vāyuruvāca|
taṃ tadāśvāsya nikṣipya naraṃ viṣṇoḥ svayaṃ prabhuḥ|
agamadbrahmasadanaṃ tau cāviviśaturgṛham|| 6.13||
ya idaṃ narajanmeha śṛṇuyādvā paṭheta vā|
sa kīrtyā parayā yukto viṣṇuloke mahīyate|| 6.14||
iti skandapurāṇe ṣaṣṭho 'adhyāyaḥ|| 6.6||

saptamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vāyuruvāca|
brahmalokaṃ samāsādya bhagavān sarvalokapaḥ|
bhaikṣyaṃ bhaikṣyam iti procya dvāre samavatiṣṭhata|| 7.1||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā vikṛtaṃ brahmā kapālakarabhūṣaṇam|
jñātvā yogena mahatā tuṣṭāva bhuvaneśvaram|| 7.2||
tasya tuṣṭastadā devo varado 'asmītyabhāṣata|
vṛṇīṣva varam avyagro yaste manasi vartate|| 7.3||
brahmovāca|
icchāmi devadeveśa tvayā cihnam idaṃ kṛtam|
yena cihnena loko 'ayaṃ cihnitaḥ syājjagatpate|| 7.4||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bhagavān vadatāṃ varaḥ|
sarvaśrutimayaṃ brahma om iti vyājahāra ha|| 7.5||
śambhorvyāhāramātreṇa vāgiyaṃ divyarūpiṇī|
niḥsṛtā vadanāddevī prahvā samavatiṣṭhata|| 7.6||
tām uvāca tadā devo vācā saṃjīvayanniva|
yasmāt tvam akṣaro bhūtvā mama vāco viniḥsṛtā|
sarvavidyādhidevī tvaṃ tasmāddevi bhaviṣyasi|| 7.7||
yasmādbrahmasaraścedaṃ mukhaṃ mama samāśritā|
tasmāt sarasvatītyeva loke khyātiṃ gamiṣyasi|| 7.8||
imaṃ lokaṃ varāmbhobhiḥ pāvayitvā ca suprabhe|
sarvā/llokāṃstārayitrī punastvaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 7.9||
yajñabhāgaṃ ca devāste dāsyanti sapitāmahāḥ|
puṇyā ca sarvasaritāṃ bhaviṣyasi na saṃśayaḥ|| 7.10||
tataḥ sā samanujñātā śaṃkareṇa vibhāvinī|
cakre brahmasaraḥ puṇyaṃ brahmaloke 'atipāvanam|| 7.11||
toyāmṛtasusampūrṇaṃ svarṇapadmopaśobhitam|
nānāpakṣigaṇākīrṇaṃ mīnasaṃkṣobhitodakam|
tato viniḥsṛtā bhūyaḥ semaṃ lokam apāvayat|| 7.12||
taṃ gṛhītvā mahādevaḥ kapālam amitaujasam|
imaṃ lokam anuprāpya deśe śreṣṭhe 'avatiṣṭhata|| 7.13||
tatra tacca mahaddivyaṃ kapālaṃ devatādhipaḥ|
sthāpayāmāsa dīptārcirgaṇānām agrataḥ prabhuḥ|| 7.14||
tat sthāpitam atho dṛṣṭvā gaṇāḥ sarve mahātmanaḥ|
anadan sumahānādaṃ nādayanto diśo daśa|
kṣubdhārṇavāśaniprakhyaṃ nabho yena vyaśīryata|| 7.15||
tena śabdena ghoreṇa asuro devakaṇṭakaḥ|
hālāhala iti khyātastaṃ deśaṃ so 'abhyagacchata|| 7.16||
amṛṣyamāṇaḥ krodhāndho durātmā yajñanāśakaḥ|
brahmadattavaraścaiva avadhyaḥ sarvajantubhiḥ|
mahiṣaśchannarūpāṇām asurāṇāṃ śatairvṛtaḥ|| 7.17||
tam āpatantaṃ sakrodhaṃ mahiṣaṃ devakaṇṭakam|
samprekṣyāha gaṇādhyakṣo gaṇān sarvān pinākinaḥ|| 7.18||
daityo 'ayaṃ gaṇapā duṣṭastrailokyasurakaṇṭakaḥ|
āyāti tvarito yūyaṃ tasmādenaṃ nihanyatha|| 7.19||
tataste gaṇapāḥ sarve samāyāntaṃ suradviṣam|
bhittvā śūlena saṃkruddhā vigatāsuṃ ca cakrire|| 7.20||
hate tasmiṃstadā devo diśaḥ sarvā avaikṣata|
tābhyaḥ piśācā vṛttāsyāḥ piśācyaśca mahābalāḥ|
abhyagacchanta deveśaṃ tābhyastaṃ vinivedayat|| 7.21||
sa tābhirupayuktaśca viniyuktaśca sarvaśaḥ|
tam eva cāpyathāvāsaṃ devādiṣṭaṃ prapedire|| 7.22||
bhakṣayanti sma mahiṣaṃ mitvā mitvā yatastu tāḥ|
kapālamātaraḥ proktāstasmāddevena dhīmatā|| 7.23||
kapālaṃ sthāpitaṃ yasmāt tasmin deśe pinākinā|
mahākapālaṃ tat tasmāt triṣu lokeṣu gadyate|| 7.24||
sthāpitasya kapālasya yathoktam abhavat tadā|
khyātaṃ śivataḍāgaṃ tat sarvapāpapramocanam|| 7.25||
āgatyātha tato brahmā devatānāṃ gaṇairvṛtaḥ|
kapardinam upāmantrya taṃ deśaṃ so 'anvagṛhṇata|| 7.26||
ardhayojanavistīrṇaṃ kṣetram etat samantataḥ|
bhaviṣyati na saṃdehaḥ siddhakṣetraṃ mahātmanaḥ|| 7.27||
śmeti hi procyate pāpaṃ kṣayaṃ śānaṃ vidurbudhāḥ|
dhyānena niyamaiścaiva śmaśānaṃ tena saṃjñitam|
guhyaṃ devātidevasya paraṃ priyam anuttamam|| 7.28||
evaṃ tatra naraḥ pāpaṃ sarvam eva prahāsyati|
trirātropoṣitaścaiva arcayitvā vṛṣadhvajam|
rājasūyāśvamedhābhyāṃ phalaṃ yat tadavāpsyati|| 7.29||
yaśca prāṇān priyāṃstatra parityakṣyati mānavaḥ|
sa guhyagaṇadevānāṃ samatāṃ samavāpsyati|| 7.30||
tataḥ sa tatra saṃsthāpya devasyārcādvayaṃ śubham|
śūleśvaraṃ mahākāyaṃ rudrasyāyatanaṃ śubham|| 7.31||
tatrābhigamanādeva kṛtvā pāpasya saṃkṣayam|
rudralokam avāpnoti sa prāhaivaṃ pitāmahaḥ|| 7.32||
yatra cāpi śirastasya ciccheda bhuvaneśvaraḥ|
kaśmīraḥ so 'abhavannāmnā deśaḥ puṇyatamaḥ sadā|| 7.33||
tato devaḥ saha gaṇai rūpaṃ vikṛtam āsthitaḥ|
paśyatāṃ sarvadevānām antardhānam agāt prabhuḥ|| 7.34||
gate ca devanāthe 'atha kapālasthānam avyayam|
sarvatīrthābhiṣekasya phalena samayojayat|| 7.35||
tadadyāpi mahaddivyaṃ sarastatra pradṛśyate|
mahākapālaṃ viprendrāḥ svargāstatrākṣayāḥ smṛtāḥ|| 7.36||
}\san
idaṃ śubhaṃ divyam adharmanāśanaṃ mahāphalaṃ sendrasurāsurārcitam|
mahākapālaṃ prakṛtopadarśanaṃ sureśalokādivigāhane hitam|| 7.37||
tapodhanaiḥ siddhagaṇaiśca saṃstutaṃ diviṣṭhatulyadvijarājamaṇḍale|
paṭhennaro yaḥ śṛṇuyācca sarvadā tripiṣṭapaṃ gacchati so 'abhinanditaḥ|| 7.38||
iti skandapurāṇe
saptamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 7.7||

aṣṭamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vāyuruvāca|
evam eṣā bhagavatī brahmalokānusāriṇī|
yuṣmākaṃ dharmasiddhyarthaṃ vedīmadhyādvyavartata|| 8.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ teṣāṃ samāpte 'atha sattre varṣasahasrike|
pravṛttāyāṃ sarasvatyām agāt tatra pitāmahaḥ|| 8.2||
brahmovāca|
bhūyo 'anyena ha sattreṇa yajadhvaṃ devam īśvaram|
yadā vo bhavitā vighnaṃ tadā niṣkalmaṣaṃ tapaḥ|| 8.3||
vighnaṃ taccaiva saṃtīrya tapastaptvā ca bhāsvaram|
yogaṃ prāpya mahadyuktāstato drakṣyatha śaṃkaram|| 8.4||
tathetyuktvā gate tasmin sattrāṇi ājahrire tadā|
bahūni vividhākārāṇyabhiyuktā mahāvratāḥ|| 8.5||
niḥsomāṃ pṛthivīṃ kṛtvā kṛtsnām etāṃ tato dvijāḥ|
rājānaṃ somam ānāyya abhiṣektum iyeṣire|| 8.6||
atha so 'api kṛtātithyaḥ adṛśyena durātmanā|
svarbhānunā hṛtaḥ somastataste duḥkhitābhavan|| 8.7||
te gatvā munayaḥ sarve kalāpagrāmavāsinaḥ|
purūravasam ānīya rājānaṃ te 'abhyaṣecayan|| 8.8||
ūcuścainaṃ mahābhāgā hṛtaḥ somo hi naḥ prabho|
kenāpi tadbhavān kṣipram ihānayatu mā ciram|| 8.9||
sa evam ukto mṛgayan na tam āsādayat prabhuḥ|
uvāca sa tadā viprān praṇamya bhayapīḍitaḥ|| 8.10||
paramaṃ yatnam āsthāya mayā somo 'abhimārgitaḥ|
na ca taṃ vedmi kenāsau kva vā nīta iti prabhuḥ|| 8.11||
tam evaṃvādinaṃ kruddhā ṛṣayaḥ saṃśitavratāḥ|
ūcuḥ sarve susaṃrabdhā ilāputraṃ mahāmatim|| 8.12||
bhavān rājā kutastrātā kṛto .asmābhirbhayārditaiḥ|
na ca nastadbhayaṃ śakto vināśayitum āśvapi|| 8.13||
viṣayeṣvatisaktātmā yogāt taṃ nānupaśyasi|
tasmādvirodham āsthāya dvijebhyo vadham āpsyasi|| 8.14||
vayam eva hi rājānam ānayiṣyāma durvidam|
tapasā svena rājendra paśya no balam uttamam|| 8.15||
tataste ṛṣayaḥ sarve tapasā dagdhakilbiṣāḥ|
astuvan vāgbhiriṣṭābhirgāyatrīṃ vedabhāvinīm|| 8.16||
stuvatāṃ tu tatasteṣāṃ gāyatrī vedabhāvinī|
rūpiṇī darśanaṃ prādāduvācedaṃ ca tān dvijān|| 8.17||
tuṣṭāsmi vatsāḥ kiṃ vo 'adya karomi varadāsmi vaḥ|
brūta tat kṛtam eveha bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|| 8.18||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ|
somo no 'apahṛto devi kenāpi sudurātmanā|
tam ānaya namaste 'astu eṣa no vara uttamaḥ|| 8.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sā tathoktā viniścitya dṛṣṭvā divyena cakṣuṣā|
śyenībhūtā jagāmāśu svarbhānum asuraṃ prati|| 8.20||
vyagrāṇām asurāṇāṃ sā gṛhītvā somam āgatā|
āgamya tānṛṣīn prāha ayaṃ somo 'abhiṣūyatām|| 8.21||
te tam āsādya ṛṣayaḥ prāpya yajñaphalaṃ mahat|
amanyanta tapo 'asmākaṃ niṣkalmaṣam iti dvijāḥ|| 8.22||
tatastatra svayaṃ brahmā saha devoragādibhiḥ|
āgatya tānṛṣīn prāha tapaḥ kuruta mā ciram|| 8.23||
te saha brahmaṇā gatvā mainākaṃ parvatottamam|
sarvairdevagaṇaiḥ sārdhaṃ tapaśceruḥ samāhitāḥ|| 8.24||
teṣāṃ kālena mahatā tapasā bhāvitātmanām|
yogapravṛttirabhavat sūkṣmayuktāstatastu te|| 8.25||
te yuktā brahmaṇā sārdham ṛṣayaḥ saha devataiḥ|
maheśvare manaḥ sthāpya niścalopalavat sthitāḥ|| 8.26||
atha teṣāṃ mahādevaḥ pinākī nīlalohitaḥ|
abhyagacchata taṃ deśaṃ vimānenārkatejasā|| 8.27||
tadbhāvabhāvitāñ{}jñātvā sadbhāvena pareṇa ha|
uvāca meghanirhrādaḥ śatadundubhinisvanaḥ|| 8.28||
bho bho sabrahmakā devāḥ saviṣṇuṛṣicāraṇāḥ|
divyaṃ cakṣuḥ prayacchāmi paśyadhvaṃ māṃ yathepsitam|| 8.29||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
apaśyanta tataḥ sarve sūryāyutasamaprabham|
vimānaṃ merusaṃkāśaṃ nānāratnavibhūṣitaṃ || 8.30||
tasya madhye 'agnikūṭaṃ ca sumahaddīptim āsthitam|
jvālāmālāparikṣiptam arcibhirupaśobhitam|| 8.31||
daṃṣṭrākarālavadanaṃ pradīptānalalocanam|
tretāgnipiṅgalajaṭaṃ bhujagābaddhamekhalam|| 8.32||
mṛṣṭakuṇḍalinaṃ caiva śūlāsaktamahākaram|
pinākinaṃ daṇḍahastaṃ mudgarāśanipāṇinam|| 8.33||
asipaṭṭisahastaṃ ca cakriṇaṃ cordhvamehanam|
akṣasūtrakaraṃ caiva duṣprekṣyam akṛtātmabhiḥ|
candrādityagrahaiścaiva kṛtasragupabhūṣaṇam|| 8.34||
tam apaśyanta te sarve devā divyena cakṣuṣā|
yaṃ dṛṣṭvā na bhavenmṛtyurmartyasyāpi kadācana|| 8.35||
tapasā viniyogayoginaḥ praṇamanto bhavam indunirmalam|
viyatīśvaradattacakṣuṣaḥ saha devairmunayo mudānvitāḥ|| 8.36||
prasamīkṣya mahāsureśakālaṃ manasā cāpi vicārya durvisahyam|
praṇamanti gatātmabhāvacintāḥ saha devairjagadudbhavaṃ stuvantaḥ|| 8.37||
iti skandapurāṇe
aṣṭamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 8.8||

navamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te dṛṣṭvā devadeveśaṃ sarve sabrahmakāḥ surāḥ|
astuvan vāgbhiriṣṭābhiḥ praṇamya vṛṣavāhanam|| 9.1||
pitāmaha uvāca|
namaḥ śivāya somāya bhaktānāṃ bhayahāriṇe|
namaḥ śūlāgrahastāya kamaṇḍaludharāya ca|| 9.2||
daṇḍine nīlakaṇṭhāya karāladaśanāya ca|
tretāgnidīptanetrāya trinetrāya harāya ca|| 9.3||
namaḥ pinākine caiva namo 'astvaśanidhāriṇe|
vyālayajñopavītāya kuṇḍalābharaṇāya ca|| 9.4||
namaścakradharāyaiva vyāghracarmadharāya ca|
kṛṣṇājinottarīyāya sarpamekhaline tathā|| 9.5||
varadātre ca rudrāya sarasvatīsṛje tathā|
somasūryarkṣamālāya akṣasūtrakarāya ca|| 9.6||
jvālāmālāsahasrāya ūrdhvaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ parvatavāsāya śirohartre ca me purā|| 9.7||
hālāhalavināśāya kapālavaradhāriṇe|
vimānavaravāhāya janakāya mamaiva ca|
varadāya variṣṭhāya śmaśānarataye namaḥ|| 9.8||
namo narasya kartre ca sthitikartre namaḥ sadā|
utpattipralayānāṃ ca kartre sarvasahāya ca|| 9.9||
ṛṣidaivatanāthāya sarvabhūtādhipāya ca|
śivaḥ saumyaśca deveśa bhava no bhaktavatsala|| 9.10||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
brahmaṇyathaivaṃ stuvati devadevaḥ sa lokapaḥ|
uvāca tuṣṭastān devānṛṣīṃśca tapasaidhitān|| 9.11||
tuṣṭo 'asmyanena vaḥ samyak tapasā ṛṣidevatāḥ|
varaṃ brūta pradāsyāmi suniścintya sa ucyatām|| 9.12||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha sarvānabhiprekṣya saṃtuṣṭāṃstapasaidhitān|
darśanenaiva viprendra brahmā vacanam abravīt|| 9.13||
brahmovāca|
yadi tuṣṭo 'asi deveśa yadi deyo varaśca naḥ|
tasmācchivaśca saumyaśca dṛśyaścaiva bhavasva naḥ|| 9.14||
sukhasaṃvyavahāryaśca nityaṃ tuṣṭamanāstathā|
sarvakāryeṣu ca sadā hitaḥ pathyaśca śaṃkaraḥ|| 9.15||
saha devyā sasūnuśca saha devagaṇairapi|
eṣa no dīyatāṃ deva varo varasahasrada|| 9.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktaḥ sa bhagavān brahmaṇā devasattamaḥ|
svakaṃ tejo mahaddivyaṃ vyasṛjat sarvayogavit|| 9.17||
ardhena tejasaḥ svasya mukhādulkāṃ sasarja ha|
tām āha bhava nārīti bhagavān viśvarūpadhṛk|| 9.18||
sākāśaṃ dyāṃ ca bhūmiṃ ca mahimnā vyāpya viṣṭhitā|
upatasthe ca deveśaṃ dīpyamānā yathā taḍit|| 9.19||
tām āha prahasan devo devīṃ kamalalocanām|
brahmāṇaṃ devi varadam ārādhaya śucismite|| 9.20||
sā tatheti pratijñāya tapastaptuṃ pracakrame|
rudraśca tānṛṣīn āha śṛṇudhvaṃ mama toṣaṇe|
phalaṃ phalavatāṃ śreṣṭhā yadbravīmi tapodhanāḥ|| 9.21||
amarā jarayā tyaktā arogā janmavarjitāḥ|
madbhaktāstapasā yuktā ihaiva ca nivatsyatha|| 9.22||
ayaṃ caivāśramaḥ śreṣṭhaḥ svarṇaśṛṅgo 'acalottamaḥ|
puṇyaṃ pavitraṃ sthānaṃ vai bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|| 9.23||
maināke parvate śreṣṭhe svarṇo 'aham abhavaṃ yataḥ|
svarṇākṣīṃ cāsṛjaṃ devīṃ svarṇākṣaṃ tena tat smṛtam|| 9.24||
svarṇākṣe ṛṣayo yūyaṃ ṣaṭkulīyāstapodhanāḥ|
nivatsyatha mayājñaptāḥ svarṇākṣaṃ vai tataśca ha|
samantādyojanaṃ kṣetraṃ pavitraṃ tanna saṃśayaḥ|| 9.25||
devagandharvacaritam apsarogaṇasevitam|
siṃhebhaśarabhākīrṇaṃ śārdūlarkṣamṛgākulam|
anekavihagākīrṇaṃ latāvṛkṣakṣupākulam|| 9.26||
brahmacārī niyamavāñjitakrodho jitendriyaḥ|
upoṣya triguṇāṃ rātriṃ caruṃ kṛtvā nivedya ca|
yatra tatra mṛtaḥ so 'api brahmaloke nivatsyati|| 9.27||
yo 'apyevam eva kāmātmā paśyet tatra vṛṣadhvajam|
gosahasraphalaṃ so 'api matprasādādavāpsyati|
niyamena mṛtaścātra mayā saha cariṣyati|| 9.28||
yāvat sthāsyanti lokāśca mainākaścāpyayaṃ giriḥ|
tāvat saha mayā devā matprasādāccariṣyatha|| 9.29||
evaṃ sa tānṛṣīnuktvā dṛṣṭvā saumyena cakṣuṣā|
paśyatām eva sarveṣāṃ tatraivāntaradhīyata|| 9.30||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyānmartyo dvijātīñchrāvayeta vā|
so 'api tatphalam āsādya carenmṛtyuvivarjitaḥ|| 9.31||
jayati jaladavāhaḥ sarvabhūtāntakālaḥ śamadamaniyatānāṃ kleśahartā yatīnām|
jananamaraṇahartā ceṣṭatāṃ dhārmikāṇāṃ vividhakaraṇayuktaḥ khecaraḥ pādacārī|| 9.32||
madanapuravidārī netradantāvapātī vigatabhayaviṣādaḥ sarvabhūtapracetāḥ|
satatam abhidadhānaścekitānātmacittaḥ karacaraṇalalāmaḥ sarvadṛgdevadevaḥ|| 9.33||
iti skandapurāṇe
navamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 9.9||

daśamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sā devī tryambakaproktā tatāpa suciraṃ tapaḥ|
nirāhārā kadācicca ekaparṇāśanā punaḥ|
vāyvāhārā punaścāpi abbhakṣā bhūya eva ca|| 10.1||
tāṃ tapaścaraṇe yuktāṃ brahmā jñātvātibhāsvarām|
uvāca brūhi tuṣṭo 'asmi devi kiṃ karavāṇi te|| 10.2||
sābravīt tryambakaṃ devaṃ patiṃ prāpyenduvarcasam|
vicareyaṃ sukhaṃ deva sarva$A$/llokān namastava|| 10.3||
brahmovāca|
na hi yena śarīreṇa kriyate paramaṃ tapaḥ|
tenaiva parameśo 'asau patiḥ śambhuravāpyate|| 10.4||
tasmāddhi yogādbhavatī dakṣasyeha prajāpateḥ|
jāyasva duhitā bhūtvā patiṃ rudram avāpsyasi|| 10.5||
tataḥ sā tadvacaḥ śrutvā yogāddevī manasvinī|
dakṣasya duhitā jajñe satī nāmātiyoginī|| 10.6||
tāṃ dakṣastryambakāyaiva dadau bhāryām aninditām|
brahmaṇo vacanādyasyāṃ mānasānasṛjat sutān|| 10.7||
ātmatulyabalān dīptāñjarāmaraṇavarjitān|
anekāni sahasrāṇi rudrāṇām amitaujasām|| 10.8||
tān dṛṣṭvā sṛjyamānāṃśca brahmā taṃ pratyaṣedhayat|
mā srākṣīrdevadeveśa prajā mṛtyuvivarjitāḥ|| 10.9||
anyāḥ sṛjasva bhadraṃ te prajā mṛtyusamanvitāḥ|
tena coktaṃ sthito 'asmīti sthāṇustena tataḥ smṛtaḥ|| 10.10||
deva uvāca|
na srakṣye mṛtyusaṃyuktāḥ prajā brahman kathaṃcana|
sthito 'asmi vacanāt te 'adya vaktavyo nāsmi te punaḥ|| 10.11||
ye tvime mānasāḥ sṛṣṭā mahātmāno mahābalāḥ|
cariṣyanti mayā sārdhaṃ sarva ete hi yājñikāḥ|| 10.12||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha kāle gate vyāsa sa dakṣaḥ śāpakāraṇāt|
anyān āhūya jāmātR̥n sadārānarcayadgṛhe|| 10.13||
satīṃ saha tryambakena nājuhāva ruṣānvitaḥ|
satī jñātvā tu tat sarvaṃ gatvā pitaram abravīt|| 10.14||
ahaṃ jyeṣṭhā variṣṭhā ca jāmātrā saha suvrata|
māṃ hitvā nārhase hyetāḥ saha bhartṛbhirarcitum|| 10.15||
krodhenātha samāviṣṭaḥ sa krodhopahatendriyaḥ|
nirīkṣya prābravīddakṣaścakṣuṣā nirdahanniva|| 10.16||
gṛhāṃśca me sapatnīkāḥ praviśanti tapodhanāḥ|
śreṣṭhāṃstasmāt sadā manye tatastānarcayāmyaham|| 10.18||
tasmādyat te karomyadya śubhaṃ vā yadi vāśubham|
pūjāṃ gṛhāṇa tāṃ putri gaccha vā yatra rocate|| 10.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sā krodhadīptāsyā na jagrāhātikopitā|
pūjām asaṃmatāṃ hīnām idaṃ covāca taṃ śubhā|| 10.20||
yasmādasaṃmatām etāṃ pūjāṃ tvaṃ kuruṣe mayi|
ślāghyāṃ caivāpyaduṣṭāṃ ca śreṣṭhāṃ māṃ garhase pitaḥ|| 10.21||
tasmādimaṃ svakaṃ dehaṃ tyajāmyeṣā tavātmajā|
asatkṛtāyāḥ kiṃ me 'adya jīvitenāśubhena ha|| 10.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ kṛtvā namaskāraṃ manasā tryambakāya ha|
uvācedaṃ susaṃrabdhā vacanaṃ vacanāraṇiḥ|| 10.23||
yatrāham upapadyeyaṃ punardehe svayecchayā|
evaṃ tatrāpyasaṃmūḍhā sambhūtā dhārmikā satī|
gaccheyaṃ dharmapatnītvaṃ tryambakasyaiva dhīmataḥ|| 10.24||
tataḥ sā dhāraṇāṃ kṛtvā āgneyīṃ sahasā satī|
dadāha vai svakaṃ dehaṃ svasamutthena vahninā|| 10.25||
tāṃ jñātvā tryambako devīṃ tathābhūtāṃ mahāyaśāḥ|
uvāca dakṣaṃ saṃgamya idaṃ vacanakovidaḥ|| 10.26||
yasmāt te ninditaścāhaṃ praśastāścetare pṛthak|
jāmātaraḥ sapatnīkāstasmādvaivasvate 'antare|
utpatsyante punaryajñe tava jāmātarastvime|| 10.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tam uvāca tadā dakṣo dūyatā hṛdayena vai|
mayā yadi sutā svā vai proktā tyaktāpi vā punaḥ|
kiṃ tavātra kṛtaṃ deva ahaṃ tasyāḥ prabhuḥ sadā|| 10.29||
yasmāt tvaṃ mām abhyaśapastasmāt tvam api śaṃkara|
bhūrloke vatsyase nityaṃ na svarloke kadācana|| 10.30||
bhāgaṃ ca tava yajñeṣu dattvā sarve dvijātayaḥ|
apaḥ sprakṣyanti sarvatra mahādeva mahādyute|| 10.31||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa devaḥ prahasaṃstam uvāca trilocanaḥ|
sarveṣām eva lokānāṃ mūlaṃ bhūrloka ucyate|| 10.32||
tam ahaṃ dhārayāmyeko lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā|
bhūrloke hi dhṛte lokāḥ sarve tiṣṭhanti śāśvatāḥ|
tasmāt tiṣṭhāmyahaṃ nityam ihaiva na tavājñayā|| 10.33||
bhāgān dattvā tathānyebhyo ditsavo me dvijātayaḥ|
apaḥ spṛśanti śuddhyarthaṃ bhāgaṃ yacchanti me tataḥ|
dattvā spṛśanti bhūyaśca dharmasyaivābhivṛddhaye|| 10.34||
yathā hi devanirmālyaṃ śucayo dhārayantyuta|
aśuciṃ spraṣṭukāmāśca tyaktvāpaḥ saṃspṛśanti ca|| 10.35||
devānām evam anyeṣāṃ ditsavo brāhmaṇarṣabhāḥ|
bhāgānapaḥ spṛśanti sma tatra kā paridevanā|| 10.36||
tvaṃ tu macchāpanirdagdho viparīto narādhamaḥ|
svasyāṃ sutāyāṃ mūḍhātmā putram utpādayiṣyasi|| 10.37||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa bhagavāñchaptvā dakṣaṃ devo jagatpatiḥ|
virarāma mahātejā jagāma ca yathāgatam|| 10.38||
candradivākaravahnisamākṣaṃ candranibhānanapadmadalākṣam|
govṛṣavāhamameyaguṇaughaṃ satatam ihenduvahaṃ praṇatāḥ smaḥ|| 10.39||
ya imaṃ dakṣaśāpāṅkaṃ devyāścaivāśarīratām|
śṛṇuyādvātha viprān vā śrāvayīta yatavrataḥ|
sarvapāpavinirmukto rudralokam avāpnuyāt|| 10.40||
iti skandapurāṇe
daśamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 10.10||

ekādaśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
kadācit svagṛhaṃ prāptaṃ kaśyapaṃ dvipadāṃ varam|
apṛcchaddhimavān praśnaṃ loke khyātikaraṃ nu kim|| 11.1||
kenākṣayāśca lokāḥ syuḥ khyātiśca paramā mune|
tathaiva cārcanīyatvaṃ satsu taṃ kathayasva me|| 11.2||
kaśyapa uvāca|
apatyena mahābāho sarvam etadavāpyate|
mama khyātirapatyena brahmaṇo ṛṣibhiśca ha|| 11.3||
kiṃ na paśyasi śailendra yato māṃ paripṛcchasi|
vartayiṣyāmi taccāpi yanme dṛṣṭaṃ purācala|| 11.4||
vārāṇasīm ahaṃ gacchannapaśyaṃ saṃsthitaṃ divi|
vimānaṃ svanavaddivyam anaupamyam aninditam|| 11.5||
tasyādhastādārtanādaṃ gartāsthāne śṛṇomyaham|
tānahaṃ tapasā jñātvā tatraivāntarhitaḥ sthitaḥ|| 11.6||
athāgāt tatra śailendra vipro niyamavāñchuciḥ|
tīrthābhiṣekapūtātmā pare tapasi saṃsthitaḥ|| 11.7||
atha sa vrajamānastu vyāghreṇābhīṣito dvijaḥ|
viveśa taṃ tadā deśaṃ sā gartā yatra bhūdhara|| 11.8||
gartāyāṃ vīraṇastambe lambamānāṃstadā munīn|
apaśyadārto duḥkhārtānapṛcchat tāṃśca sa dvijaḥ|| 11.9||
ke yūyaṃ vīraṇastambe lambamānā hyadhomukhāḥ|
duḥkhitāḥ kena mokṣaśca yuṣmākaṃ bhavitānaghāḥ|| 11.10||
pitara ūcuḥ|
vayaṃ te 'akṛtapuṇyasya pitaraḥ sapitāmahāḥ|
prapitāmahāśca kliśyāmastava duṣṭena karmaṇā|| 11.11||
narako 'ayaṃ mahābhāga gartārūpaṃ samāsthitaḥ|
tvaṃ cāpi vīraṇastambastvayi lambāmahe vayam|| 11.12||
yāvat tvaṃ jīvase vipra tāvadeva vayaṃ sthitāḥ|
mṛte tvayi gamiṣyāmo narakaṃ pāpacetasaḥ|| 11.13||
yadi tvaṃ dārasaṃyogaṃ kṛtvāpatyaṃ guṇottaram|
utpādayasi tenāsmān mucyema vayam ekaśaḥ|| 11.14||
nānyena tapasā putra na tīrthānāṃ phalena ca|
tat kuruṣva mahābuddhe tārayasva pitR̥n bhayāt|| 11.15||
sa tatheti pratijñāya ārādhya ca vṛṣadhvajam|
pitR̥n gartāt samuddhṛtya gaṇapān pracakāra ha|| 11.16||
svayaṃ ca rudradayitaḥ sukeśo nāma nāmataḥ|
saṃmato balavāṃścaiva rudrasya gaṇapo 'abhavat|| 11.17||
tasmāt kṛtvā tapo ghoram apatyaṃ guṇavattaram|
utpādayasva śailendra tataḥ kīrtim avāpsyasi|| 11.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto ṛṣiṇā śailendro niyame sthitaḥ|
tapaścakāra vipulaṃ yena brahmā tutoṣa ha|| 11.19||
tam āgatya tadā brahmā varado 'asmītyabhāṣata|
brūhi tuṣṭo 'asmi te śaila tapasānena suvrata|| 11.20||
himavānuvāca|
bhagavan putram icchāmi guṇaiḥ sarvairalaṃkṛtam|
etadvaraṃ prayacchasva yadi tuṣṭo 'asi naḥ prabho|| 11.21||
brahmovāca|
kanyā bhavitrī śailendra sutā te varavarṇinī|
yasyāḥ prabhāvāt sarvatra kīrtim āpsyasi puṣkalām|| 11.22||
arcitaḥ sarvadevānāṃ tīrthakoṭīsamāvṛtaḥ|
pāvanaścaiva puṇyaśca devānām api sarvataḥ|
jyeṣṭhā ca sā bhavitrī te anye cānu tataḥ śubhe|| 11.23||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā tato brahmā tatraivāntaradhīyata|
so 'api kālena śailendro menāyām upapādayat|
aparṇām ekaparṇāṃ ca tathā cāpyekapāṭalām|| 11.24||
nyagrodham ekaparṇā tu pāṭalaṃ caikapāṭalā|
āśrite dve aparṇā tu aniketā tapo 'acarat|
śataṃ varṣasahasrāṇāṃ duścaraṃ devadānavaiḥ|| 11.25||
āhāram ekaparṇena saikaparṇā samācarat|
pāṭalena tathaikena vidadhātyekapāṭalā|| 11.26||
pūrṇe pūrṇe sahasre tu āhāraṃ tena cakratuḥ|
aparṇā tu nirāhārā tāṃ mātā pratyabhāṣata|
niṣedhayantī hyu meti mātṛsnehena duḥkhitā|| 11.27||
sā tathoktā tadā mātrā devī duścaracāriṇī|
tenaiva nāmnā lokeṣu vikhyātā surapūjitā|| 11.28||
etat tattrikumārīṇāṃ jagat sthāvarajaṅgamam|
etāsāṃ tapasā labdhaṃ yāvadbhūmirdhariṣyati|| 11.29||
tapaḥśarīrāstāḥ sarvāstisro yogabalānvitāḥ|
sarvāścaiva mahābhāgāḥ sarvāśca sthirayauvanāḥ|| 11.30||
tā lokamātaraścaiva brahmacāriṇya eva ca|
anugṛhṇanti lokāṃśca tapasā svena sarvadā|| 11.31||
umā tāsāṃ variṣṭhā ca śreṣṭhā ca varavarṇinī|
mahāyogabalopetā mahādevam upasthitā|| 11.32||
dattakaścośanā tasyāḥ putraḥ sa bhṛgunandanaḥ|
asitasyaikaparṇā tu devalaṃ suṣuve sutam|| 11.33||
yā tu tāsāṃ kumārīṇāṃ tṛtīyā hyekapāṭalā|
putraṃ śataśalākasya jaigīṣavyam upasthitā|
tasyāpi śaṅkhalikhitau smṛtau putrāvayonijau|| 11.34||
umā tu yā mayā tubhyaṃ kīrtitā varavarṇinī|
atha tasyāstapoyogāt trailokyam akhilaṃ tadā|
pradhūpitaṃ samālakṣya brahmā vacanam abravīt|| 11.35||
brahmovāca|
devi kiṃ tapasā lokāṃstāpayasyatiśobhane|
tvayā sṛṣṭam idaṃ viśvaṃ mā kṛtvā tadvināśaya|| 11.36||
tvaṃ hi dhārayase lokānimān sarvān svatejasā|
brūhi kiṃ te jaganmātaḥ prārthitaṃ samprasīda naḥ|| 11.37||
devyuvāca|
yadarthaṃ tapaso hyasya caraṇaṃ me pitāmaha|
jānīṣe tat tvam etanme tataḥ pṛcchasi kiṃ punaḥ|| 11.38||
brahmovāca|
yadarthaṃ devi tapasā śrāmyase lokabhāvani|
sa tvāṃ svayaṃ samāgamya ihaiva varayiṣyati|| 11.39||
sarvadevapatiḥ śreṣṭhaḥ sarvalokeśvareśvaraḥ|
vayaṃ sadevā yasyeśe vaśyāḥ kiṃkaravādinaḥ|| 11.40||
sa devadevaḥ parameśvareśvaraḥ svayaṃ tavāyāsyati lokapo 'antikam|
udārarūpo vikṛtābhirūpavān samānarūpo na hi yasya kasyacit|| 11.41||
maheśvaraḥ parvatalokavāsī carācareśaḥ prathamo 'aprameyaḥ|
vinendunā indusamānavaktro vibhīṣaṇaṃ rūpam ihāsthito 'agram|| 11.42||
iti skandapurāṇe
ekādaśo .adhyāyaḥ|| 11.11||

dvādaśamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devo brahmā tām āha susvaram|
devi yenaiva sṛṣṭāsi manasā yastvayā vṛtaḥ|
sa bhartā tava deveśo bhavitā mā tapaḥ kṛthāḥ|| 12.1||
tataḥ pradakṣiṇaṃ kṛtvā brahmā vyāsa gireḥ sutām|
jagāmādarśanaṃ tasyāḥ sā cāpi virarāma ha|| 12.2||
sā devī yuktam ityevam uktvā svasyāśramasya ha|
dvāri jātam aśokaṃ vai samupāśritya saṃsthitā|| 12.3||
athāgāccandratilakastridaśārtiharo haraḥ|
vikṛtaṃ rūpam āsthāya hrasvo bāhuka eva ca|| 12.4||
vibhugnanāsiko bhūtvā kubjaḥ keśāntapiṅgalaḥ|
uvāca vikṛtāsyaśca devi tvāṃ varayāmyaham|| 12.5||
athomā yogasaṃsiddhā jñātvā śaṃkaram āgatam|
antarbhāvaviśuddhā sā kriyānuṣṭhānalipsayā|| 12.6||
tam uvācārghyam ānāyya madhuparkeṇa caiva hi|
sampūjya sasukhāsīnaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ brāhmaṇapriyā|| 12.7||
devyuvāca|
bhagavannasvatantrāsmi pitā me 'astyaraṇī tathā|
tau prabhū mama dāne vai kanyāhaṃ dvijapuṃgava|| 12.8||
gatvā yācasva pitaraṃ mama śailendram avyayam|
sa ceddadāti māṃ vipra tubhyaṃ tadrucitaṃ mama|| 12.9||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devastathaiva vikṛtaḥ prabhuḥ|
uvāca śailarājaṃ tam umāṃ me yaccha śailarāṭ|| 12.10||
sa taṃ vikṛtarūpeṇa jñātvā rudram athāvyayam|
bhītaḥ śāpācca vimanā idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 12.11||
bhagavan nāvamanyāmi brāhmaṇān bhūmidaivatān|
manīṣitaṃ tu yat pūrvaṃ tacchṛṇuṣva mahātapaḥ|| 12.12||
svayaṃvaro me duhiturbhavitā viprapūjitaḥ|
varayedyaṃ svayaṃ tatra sa bhartāsyā bhavediti|| 12.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tacchrutvā śailavacanaṃ bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|
devyāḥ samīpam āgatya idam āha mahāmanāḥ|| 12.14||
devi pitrā tavājñaptaḥ svayaṃvara iti śrutam|
tatra tvaṃ varayitrī yaṃ sa te bhartā kilānaghe|| 12.15||
tadāpṛcche gamiṣyāmi durlabhā tvaṃ varānane|
rūpavantaṃ samutsṛjya vṛṇīthā mādṛśaṃ katham|| 12.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tenoktā sā tadā tatra bhāvayantī tadīritam|
bhāvaṃ ca rudranihitaṃ prasādaṃ manasastathā|| 12.17||
samprāpyovāca deveśaṃ mā te bhūdbuddhiranyathā|
ahaṃ tvāṃ varayiṣyāmi nānyadbhūtaṃ kathaṃcana|| 12.18||
atha vā te 'asti saṃdeho mayi vipra kathaṃcana|
ihaiva tvāṃ mahābhāga varayāmi manoratham|| 12.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
gṛhītvā stabakaṃ sā tu hastābhyāṃ tatra saṃsthitam|
skandhe śambhoḥ samādāya devī prāha vṛto 'asi me|| 12.20||
tataḥ sa bhagavān devastathā devyā vṛtastadā|
uvāca tam aśokaṃ vai vācā saṃjīvayanniva|| 12.21||
yasmāt tava supuṣpeṇa stabakena vṛto hyaham|
tasmāt tvaṃ jarayā tyaktaḥ amaraḥ sambhaviṣyasi|| 12.22||
kāmarūpaḥ kāmapuṣpaḥ kāmago dayito mama|
sarvābharaṇapuṣpāḍhyaḥ sarvavṛkṣaphalopagaḥ|| 12.23||
sarvānnabhakṣadaścaiva amṛtasrava eva ca|
sarvagandhaśca devyāstvaṃ bhaviṣyasi dṛḍhaṃ priyaḥ|
nirbhayaḥ sarvalokeṣu cariṣyasi sunirvṛtaḥ|| 12.24||
āśramaṃ caivam atyarthaṃ citrakūṭeti viśrutam|
yo 'abhiyāsyati puṇyārthī so 'aśvamedham avāpsyati|
yatra tatra mṛtaścāpi brahmalokaṃ gamiṣyati|| 12.25||
yaścātra niyamairyuktaḥ prāṇān samyak parityajet|
sa devyāstapasā yukto mahāgaṇapatirbhavet|| 12.26||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā tadā deva āpṛcchya himavatsutām|
antardadhe jagatsraṣṭā sarvabhūtapa īśvaraḥ|| 12.27||
sāpi devī gate tasmin bhagavatyamitātmani|
tata evonmukhī sthitvā śilāyāṃ saṃviveśa ha|| 12.28||
unmukhī sā gate tasmin maheṣvāse prajāpatau|
niśeva candrarahitā sā babhau vimanāstadā|| 12.29||
atha śuśrāva sā śabdaṃ bālasyārtasya śailajā|
sarasyudakasampūrṇe samīpe cāśramasya ha|| 12.30||
sa kṛtvā bālarūpaṃ tu devadevaḥ svayaṃ śivaḥ|
krīḍāhetoḥ saromadhye grāhagrasto 'abhavat tadā|| 12.31||
yogamāyām athāsthāya prapañcodbhavakāraṇam|
tadrūpaṃ saraso madhye kṛtvedaṃ samabhāṣata|
trātu māṃ kaścidetyeha grāheṇa hṛtacetasam|| 12.32||
dhik kaṣṭaṃ bāla evāham aprāptārthamanorathaḥ|
yāsyāmi nidhanaṃ vaktre grāhasyāsya durātmanaḥ|| 12.33||
śocāmi na svakaṃ dehaṃ grāhagrasto 'api duḥkhitaḥ|
yathā śocāmi pitaraṃ mātaraṃ ca tapasvinīm|| 12.34||
māṃ śrutvā grāhavadane prāptaṃ nidhanam utsukau|
priyaputrāvekaputrau prāṇān nūnaṃ vihāsyataḥ|| 12.35||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śrutvā tu devī taṃ nādaṃ viprasyārtasya śobhanā|
utthāya pradrutā tatra yatra tiṣṭhatyasau dvijaḥ|| 12.36||
sāpaśyadinduvadanā bālakaṃ cārurūpiṇam|
grāheṇa grasyamānaṃ taṃ vepamānam avasthitam|| 12.37||
so 'api grāhavaraḥ śrīmān dṛṣṭvā devīm upāgatām|
taṃ gṛhītvā drutaṃ yāto madhyaṃ sarasa eva ha|| 12.38||
sa kṛṣyamāṇastejasvī nādam ārtaṃ tadākarot|
athāha devī duḥkhārtā bālaṃ dṛṣṭvā mahāvratā|| 12.39||
grāharāja mahāsattva bālakaṃ hyekaputrakam|
visṛjainaṃ mahādaṃṣṭra kṣipraṃ bhīmaparākrama|| 12.40||
grāha uvāca|
yo devi divase ṣaṣṭhe prathamaṃ samupaiti mām|
sa āhāro mama purā vihito lokakartṛbhiḥ|| 12.41||
so 'ayaṃ mama mahābhāge ṣaṣṭhe 'ahani girīndraje|
brahmaṇā vihito nūnaṃ nainaṃ mokṣye kathaṃcana|| 12.42||
devyuvāca|
yanmayā himavacchṛṅge caritaṃ tapa uttamam|
tena bālam imaṃ muñca grāharāja namo 'astu te|| 12.43||
grāha uvāca|
mā vyayaṃ tapaso devi kārṣīḥ śailendranandane|
nainaṃ mocayituṃ śakto devarājo 'api sa svayam|| 12.44||
mahyam īśena tuṣṭena śarveṇogreṇa śūlinā|
amaratvam avadhyatvam akṣayaṃ balam eva ca|| 12.45||
svayaṃgrahaṇamokṣaśca jñānaṃ caivāvyayaṃ punaḥ|
dattaṃ tato bravīmi tvāṃ nāyaṃ mokṣam avāpsyati|| 12.46||
atha vā te kṛpā devi bhṛśaṃ bāle śubhānane|
bravīmi yat kuru tathā tato mokṣam avāpsyati|| 12.47||
devyuvāca|
grāhādhipa vadasvāśu yat satām avigarhitam|
tat kṛtaṃ nātra saṃdeho mānyā me brāhmaṇā dṛḍham|| 12.48||
grāha uvāca|
yat kṛtaṃ vai tapaḥ kiṃcidbhavatyā svalpam antaśaḥ|
tat sarvaṃ me prayacchasva tato mokṣam avāpsyati|| 12.49||
devyuvāca|
janmaprabhṛti yat puṇyaṃ mahāgrāha kṛtaṃ mayā|
tat te sarvaṃ mayā dattaṃ bālaṃ muñca mamāgrataḥ|| 12.50||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
prajajvāla tato grāhastapasā tena bṛṃhitaḥ|
āditya iva madhyāhne durnirīkṣyastadābhavat|| 12.51||
uvāca cedaṃ tuṣṭātmā devīṃ lokasya dhāriṇīm|
devi kiṃ kṛtam etat te aniścitya mahāvrate|
tapaso hyarjanaṃ duḥkhaṃ tasya tyāgo na śasyate|| 12.52||
gṛhāṇa tapa etacca bālaṃ cemaṃ śucismite|
tuṣṭo 'asmi te viprabhaktyā varaṃ tasmāddadāmi te|| 12.53||
sā tvevamuktā grāheṇa uvācedaṃ mahāvratā|
suniścitya mahāgrāha kṛtaṃ bālasya mokṣaṇam|
na viprebhyastapaḥ śreṣṭhaṃ śreṣṭhā me brāhmaṇā matāḥ|| 12.54||
dattvā cāhaṃ na gṛhṇāmi grāhendra viditaṃ hi te|
na hi kaścinnaro grāha pradattaṃ punarāharet|| 12.55||
dattam etanmayā tubhyaṃ nādadāni hi tat punaḥ|
tvayyeva ramatām etadbālaścāyaṃ vimucyatām|| 12.56||
tathoktastāṃ praśasyātha muktvā bālaṃ namasya ca|
devīm ādityasadbhāsaṃ tatraivāntaradhīyata|| 12.57||
bālo 'api sarasastīre mukto grāheṇa vai tadā|
svapnalabdha ivārthaughastatraivāntaradhīyata|| 12.58||
tapaso 'atha vyayaṃ matvā devī himagirīndrajā|
bhūya eva tapaḥ kartum ārebhe yatnam āsthitā|| 12.59||
kartukāmāṃ tapo bhūyo jñātvā tāṃ śaṃkaraḥ svayam|
provāca vacanaṃ vyāsa mā kṛthāstapa ityuta|| 12.60||
mahyam etat tapo devi tvayā dattaṃ mahāvrate|
tenaivam akṣayaṃ tubhyaṃ bhaviṣyati sahasradhā|| 12.61||
iti labdhvā varaṃ devī tapaso 'akṣayyam uttamam|
svayaṃvaram udīkṣantī tasthau prītimudāyutā|| 12.62||
idaṃ paṭhedyo hi naraḥ sadaiva bālānubhāvācaraṇaṃ hi śambhoḥ|
sa dehabhedaṃ samavāpya pūto bhavedgaṇastasya kumāratulyaḥ|| 12.63||
iti skandapurāṇe dvādaśamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 12.12||
EOF

trayodaśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vistṛte himavatpṛṣṭhe vimānaśatasaṃkule|
abhavat sa tu kālena śailaputryāḥ svayaṃvaraḥ|| 13.1||
atha parvatarājo 'asau himavān dhyānakovidaḥ|
duhiturdevadevena jñātvā tadabhimantritam|| 13.2||
jānannapi mahāśailaḥ samācārakriyepsayā|
svayaṃvaraṃ tato devyāḥ sarvalokeṣvaghoṣayat|| 13.3||
devadānavasiddhānāṃ sarvalokanivāsinām|
vṛṇuyāt parameśānaṃ samakṣaṃ yena me sutā|| 13.4||
tadeva sukṛtaṃ ślāghyaṃ mamābhyudayasaṃmatam|
iti saṃcintya śailendraḥ kṛtvā hṛdi maheśvaram|| 13.5||
ābrahmakeṣu lokeṣu devyāḥ śailendrasattamaḥ|
kṛtvā ratnākulaṃ deśaṃ svayaṃvaram acīkarat|| 13.6||
athaivam āghoṣitamātra eva svayaṃvare vyāsa mahīdhraputryāḥ|
devādayaḥ sarvajagannivāsāḥ samāyayurdivyagṛhītaveṣāḥ|| 13.7||
praphullapadmāsanasaṃniviṣṭaḥ siddhairvṛto yogibhiraprameyaiḥ|
vijñāpitastena mahīdhrarājñā pitāmahastatra samājagāma|| 13.8||
akṣṇāṃ sahasraṃ surarāṭ sa bibhraddivyāṅgahārasragudāttarūpaḥ|
airāvataṃ sarvagajendramukhyaṃ sravanmadāsārakṛtapravāham|
āruhya sarvāmararāṭ sa vajraṃ bibhrat samāgāt purataḥ surāṇām|| 13.9||
tejaḥpratāpādhikadivyarūpaḥ prodbhāsayan sarvadiśo vivasvān|
haimaṃ vimānaṃ sacalatpatākam āruhya āgāt tvaritaṃ javena|| 13.10||
maṇipradīptojjvalakuṇḍalaśca vahnyarkatejaḥpratime vimāne|
samabhyagāt kaśyapaviprasūnurāditya āgādbhaganāmadhārī|| 13.11||
pīnāṅgayaṣṭiḥ sukṛtāṅgahārastejobalājñāsadṛśaprabhāvaḥ|
daṇḍaṃ samādāya kṛtānta āgādāruhya bhīmaṃ mahiṣaṃ javena|| 13.12||
mahāmahīdhrocchrayapīnagātraḥ svarṇādiratnācitacāruveṣaḥ|
samīraṇaḥ sarvajagadvibhartā vimānam āruhya samabhyagāddhi|| 13.13||
saṃtāpayan sarvasurāsureśāṃstejodhikastejasi saṃniviśya|
vahniḥ samabhyetya surendramadhye jvalan pratasthau varaveṣadhārī|| 13.14||
nānāmaṇiprajvalitāṅgayaṣṭirjagaccarandivyavimānam agryam|
āruhya sarvadraviṇādhipeśaḥ sa rājarājastvarito 'abhyagācca|| 13.15||
āpyāyayan sarvasurāsureśān kāntyā ca veṣeṇa ca cārurūpaḥ|
jvalanmahāratnavicitrarūpaṃ vimānam āruhya śaśī samāgāt|| 13.16||
śyāmāṅgayaṣṭiḥ suvicitraveṣaḥ sarvasragābaddhasugandhamālī|
tārkṣyaṃ samāruhya mahīdhrakalpaṃ gadādharo 'asau tvaritaṃ sametaḥ|| 13.17||
tathāśvinau devabhiṣagvarau tu ekaṃ vimānaṃ tvarayābhiruhya|
manoharāvujjvalacāruveṣau ājagmaturdevasadaḥ suvīrau|| 13.18||
śeṣaḥ sahasraṃ sphuradagnivarṇaṃ bibhrat sphaṭānāṃ jvalanārkatejāḥ|
sārdhaṃ sa nāgairaparairmahātmā vimānam āruhya samabhyagācca|| 13.19||
diteḥ sutānāṃ ca mahāsurāṇāṃ vahnyarkaśakrānilatulyabhāsām|
varānurūpaṃ pravidhāya veṣaṃ vṛndaṃ samāgāt purataḥ surāṇām|| 13.20||
gandharvarājaḥ sa ca cārurūpī divyaṅgamo divyavimānacārī|
gandharvasaṃghaiḥ sahito 'apsarobhiḥ śakrājñayā tatra samājagāma|| 13.21||
anye ca devāstridivaukaseśāḥ pṛthak pṛthak cārugṛhītaveṣāḥ|
ājagmurāruhya vimānapṛṣṭhaṃ gandharvayakṣoragakiṃnarāśca|| 13.22||
śacīpatistatra surendramadhye rājādhikārādhikalakṣyamūrtiḥ|
ājñābalaiśvaryakṛtapramoho vṛthādhikaṃ yatnam upācakāra|| 13.23||
hetustrilokasya jagatprasūtermātā ca teṣāṃ sasurāsurāṇām|
patnī ca śambhoḥ puruṣasya dhāmno gītā purāṇe prakṛtiḥ parārthā|
dakṣasya kopāddhimavadgṛhaṃ sā kāryārtham āgāt parameśapatnī|| 13.24||
evaṃ yatastāṃ na viduḥ sureśā mohastatastān para āviveśa|
varārtham ājagmurato vimūḍhā īśena yasmādvṛḍitāḥ kṛtāste|| 13.25||
tataḥ pranṛttābhirathāpsarobhirgandharvasaṃghaiśca sugītaśabdaiḥ|
sthitaiśca nānāvidharūpaveṣairdevāsurāditridivaukasaṃghaiḥ|| 13.26||
vimānapṛṣṭhe maṇihemacitre sthitā calaccāmaravījitāṅgī|
sarvartupuṣpāṃ susugandhamālāṃ pragṛhya devī prasabhaṃ pratasthe|| 13.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
mālāṃ pragṛhya devyāṃ tu sthitāyāṃ devasaṃsadi|
śakrādyairāgatairdevaiḥ svayaṃvaram upāgataiḥ|| 13.28||
devyā jijñāsayā śambhurbhūtvā pañcaśikhaḥ śiśuḥ|
utsaṅgatalasaṃsupto babhūva sahasā vibhuḥ|| 13.29||
akasmādatha taṃ devī śiśuṃ pañcaśikhaṃ sthitam|
jñātvā yogasamādhānājjahṛṣe prītisaṃyutā|| 13.30||
atha sā śuddhasaṃkalpā kāṅkṣitaprāptasatphalā|
nirvṛteva tadā tasthau kṛtvā hṛdi tam eva tu|| 13.31||
tato dṛṣṭvā śiśuṃ devā devyā utsaṅgavartinam|
ko 'ayam atreti saṃmantrya cukrudhurbhṛśam ārditāḥ|| 13.32||
vajram ākārayat tasya bāhum utkṣipya vṛtrahā|
sa bāhurutthitastasya tathaiva samatiṣṭhata|| 13.33||
stambhitaḥ śiśurūpeṇa devadevena śambhunā|
vajraṃ kṣeptuṃ na śaśāka bāhuṃ cālayituṃ na ca|| 13.34||
bhago nāma tato deva ādityaḥ kāśyapo balī|
utkṣipya muśalaṃ dīptaṃ kṣeptum aicchadvimohitaḥ|
tasyāpi bhagavān bāhuṃ tathaivāstambhayat tadā|| 13.35||
śiraḥ prakampayan viṣṇuḥ sakrodhastam avaikṣata|
tasyāpi śiraso devaḥ khālityaṃ pracakāra ha|| 13.36||
pūṣā dantān daśan dantaiḥ śarvam aikṣata mohitaḥ|
tasyāpi daśanāḥ peturdṛṣṭamātrasya śambhunā|| 13.37||
yamasya stambhito daṇḍastejo vahneḥ śaśeḥ prabhā|
balaṃ vāyostathānyeṣāṃ tasmin sarvadivaukasām|
balaṃ tejaśca yogaṃ ca tathaivāstambhayadvibhuḥ|| 13.38||
atha teṣu sthiteṣvevaṃ manyumatsu sureṣu tu|
brahmā paramasaṃvigno dhyānam āsthāya sādaram|
bubudhe devadeveśam umotsaṅgasamāsthitam|| 13.39||
sa buddhvā parameśānaṃ śīghram utthāya sādaram|
vavande caraṇau śambhorastuvacca pitāmahaḥ|
paurāṇaiḥ sāmasaṃgītaiḥ puṇyākhyairguhyanāmabhiḥ|| 13.40||
ajastvam amaro deva sraṣṭā hartā vibhuḥ paraḥ|
pradhānapuruṣastattvaṃ brahma dhyeyaṃ tadakṣayam|| 13.41||
amṛtaṃ paramātmā ca īśvaraḥ kāraṇaṃ mahat|
brahmakṛt prakṛteḥ sraṣṭā sarvasṛk parameśvaraḥ|| 13.42||
iyaṃ ca prakṛtirdevī sadā te sṛṣṭikāraṇam|
patnīrūpaṃ samāsthāya jagatkāraṇam āgatā|| 13.43||
namastubhyaṃ sadeśāna devyāścaiva sadā namaḥ|
prasādāt tava deveśa niyogācca mayā prajāḥ|| 13.44||
devādyāsta ime sṛṣṭā mūḍhāstvadyogamohitāḥ|
kuru prasādam eteṣāṃ yathāpūrvaṃ bhavantvime|| 13.45||
tata evaṃ tadā brahmā vijñāpya parameśvaram|
stambhitān sarvadevāṃstānidam āha mahādyutiḥ|| 13.46||
mūḍhāḥ stha devatāḥ sarve nainaṃ budhyata śaṃkaram|
devadevam ihāyātaṃ mamaivotpattikāraṇam|| 13.47||
ayaṃ rudro mahādevaḥ śarvo bhīmaḥ kapardimān|
ugra īśāna ātmā ca ajaḥ śaṃkara eva ca|| 13.48||
devadevaḥ paraṃ dhāma īśaḥ paśupatiḥ patiḥ|
jagatsraṣṭā jagaddhartā jagatsaṃsthitikāraṇam|| 13.49||
gacchadhvaṃ śaraṇaṃ śīghram evam evāmareśvarāḥ|
sārdhaṃ mayaiva deveśaṃ paramātmānam avyayam|| 13.50||
tataste stambhitāḥ sarve tathaiva tridivaukasaḥ|
praṇemurmanasā śarvaṃ bhāvaśuddhena cetasā|| 13.51||
atha teṣāṃ prasanno 'abhūddevadevo maheśvaraḥ|
yathāpūrvaṃ cakārāśu devatānāṃ tanūstadā|| 13.52||
tata evaṃ pravṛtte tu sarvadevanivāraṇe|
vapuścakāra deveśastryakṣaṃ paramam adbhutam|
tejasā yasya devāste cakṣuraprārthayan vibhum|| 13.53||
tebhyaḥ paramakaṃ cakṣuḥ svavapurdṛṣṭiśaktimat|
prādāt paramadeveśaḥ apaśyaṃste tadā prabhum|| 13.54||
te dṛṣṭvā parameśānaṃ tṛtīyekṣaṇadhāriṇam|
brahmādyā nemire tūrṇaṃ sarva eva sureśvarāḥ|| 13.55||
tasya devī tadā hṛṣṭā samakṣaṃ tridivaukasām|
pādayoḥ sthāpayāmāsa sragmālām amitadyuteḥ|| 13.56||
sādhu sādhviti samprocya devatāste punarvibhum|
saha devyā namaścakruḥ śirobhirbhūtalāśritaiḥ|| 13.57||
athāsminnantare vyāsa brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
himavantaṃ mahāśailam idam āha mahādyutiḥ|| 13.58||
ślāghyaḥ pūjyaśca vandyaśca sarveṣāṃ nastvam adya hi|
śarveṇa saha sambandho yasya te 'abhūdayaṃ mahān|
kriyatāṃ cāśu udvāhaḥ kimarthaṃ sthīyate param|| 13.59||
tataḥ praṇamya himavāṃstaṃ devaṃ pratyabhāṣata|
tvam eva kāraṇaṃ deva yena śarvādayaṃ mama|| 13.60||
prasādaḥ sahasotpanno hetuścāpi tvam eva hi|
udvāhaṃ tu yathā yādṛk tadvidhatsva pitāmaha|| 13.61||
tata evaṃ vacaḥ śrutvā girirājñaḥ pitāmahaḥ|
udvāhaḥ kriyatāṃ deva iti devam uvāca ha|
tam āha śaṃkaro devaṃ yatheṣṭam iti lokapaḥ|| 13.62||
tatkṣaṇācca tato vyāsa brahmaṇā kalpitaṃ puram|
udvāhārthaṃ maheśasya nānāratnopaśobhitam|| 13.63||
ratnāni maṇayaścitrā hema mauktikam eva ca|
mūrtimanta upāgamya alaṃcakruḥ purottamam|| 13.64||
citrā mārakatī bhūmiḥ sauvarṇastambhaśobhitā|
bhāsvatsphaṭikabhittībhirmuktāhārapralambitā|| 13.65||
tasmiñchivapure ramye udvāhārthaṃ vinirmite|
śuśubhe devadevasya maheśasya mahātmanaḥ|| 13.66||
somādityau samaṃ tatra bhāsayantau mahāmaṇī|
saurabheyaṃ manoramyaṃ gandham āghrāya mārutaḥ|
pravavau sukhasaṃsparśa īśe bhaktiṃ prasādayan|| 13.67||
samudrāstatra catvāraḥ śakrādyāśca surottamāḥ|
devanadyo mahānadyaḥ siddhā munaya eva ca|| 13.68||
gandharvāpsarasaḥ sarve nāgā yakṣāḥ sarākṣasāḥ|
guhyakāḥ khecarāścānye kiṃnarā devacāraṇāḥ|| 13.69||
tumbururnārado hāhā hūhū caiva tu sāmagāḥ|
ratnāni ādāya vādyāṃśca tatrājagmustadā puram|| 13.70||
ṛṣayaḥ kṛtsnaśastatra vedagītāṃstapodhanāḥ|
puṇyān vaivāhikān mantrāñjepuḥ saṃhṛṣṭamānasāḥ|| 13.71||
jagato mātaraḥ sarvā devakanyāśca kṛtsnaśaḥ|
gāyanti hṛṣitāḥ sarvā udvāhe parameṣṭhinaḥ|| 13.72||
ṛtavaḥ ṣaṭ samaṃ tatra nānāgandhasukhāvahāḥ|
udvāhaḥ śaṃkarasyeti mūrtimanta upasthitāḥ|| 13.73||
nīlajīmūtasaṃghātamandradhvānapraharṣitaiḥ|
kekāyamānaiḥ śikhibhirnṛtyamānaiśca sarvaśaḥ|| 13.74||
vilolapiṅgalaspaṣṭavidyullekhāvabhāsitā|
kumudāpītaśuklābhirbalākābhiśca śobhitā|| 13.75||
pratyagrasaṃjātaśilīndhrakandalā latādrumābhyudgatacārupallavā|
śubhāmbudhārāpraṇayaprabodhitairmadālasairbhekagaṇaiśca nāditā|| 13.76||
priyeṣu mānonnatamānasānāṃ suniścitānām api kāminīnām|
mayūrakekābhirutaiḥ kṣaṇena manoharairmānavibhaṅgakartrī|| 13.77||
tathā trivarṇojjvalacārumūrtinā śaśāṅkalekhākuṭilena sarvataḥ|
payodasaṃghātasamīpavartinā mahendracāpena bhṛśaṃ virājitā|| 13.78||
vicitrapuṣpasparśāt sugandhibhirghanāmbusamparkatayā suśītalaiḥ|
vikampayantī pavanairmanoharaiḥ surāṅganānām alakāvalīḥ śubhāḥ|| 13.79||
garjatpayodasthagitendubimbā navāmbusekodgatacārudūrvā|
nirīkṣitā sādaram utsukābhirniśvāsadhūmraṃ pathikāṅganābhiḥ|| 13.80||
haṃsanūpuraśabdāḍhyā samunnatapayodharā|
caladvidyullatākāñcī spaṣṭapadmavilocanā|| 13.81||
asitajaladavṛndadhvānavitrastahaṃsā vimalasaliladhārāpātanamrotpalāgrā|
surabhikusumareṇukḷptasarvāṅgaśobhā giriduhitṛvivāhe prāvṛḍāgādvibhūtyai|| 13.82||
meghakañcukanirmuktā padmakośodgatastanī|
haṃsanūpuranirhrādā sarvaramyadigantarā|| 13.83||
vistīrṇapulinaśroṇī kūjatsārasamekhalā|
praphullendīvarābhogavilocanamanoharā|| 13.84||
pakvabimbādharapuṭā kundadantaprahāsinī|
navaśyāmālatāśyāmaromarājīpariṣkṛtā|| 13.85||
candrāṃśuhāravaryeṇa saudhoraḥsthalasarpiṇā|
prahlādayantī cetāṃsi sarveṣāṃ tridivaukasām|| 13.86||
samadālikulodgītamadhurasvarabhāṣiṇī|
calatkumudasaṃghātacārukuṇḍalaśobhinī|| 13.87||
raktāśokāgraśākhotthapallavāṅgulidhāriṇī|
tatpuṣpasaṃcayamayairvāsobhiḥ samalaṃkṛtā|| 13.88||
raktotpalāgracaraṇā jātīpuṣpanakhāvalī|
kadalīstambhacārūruḥ śaśāṅkavadanā tathā|| 13.89||
padmakiñjalkasampṛktapavanāgrakaraiḥ surān|
premṇā spṛśantī kānteva śaradāgānmanoramā|| 13.90||
nirmuktāsitameghakañcukapuṭā pūrṇendubimbānanā
atyarthaśītalāmbhobhiḥ plāvayantau gireḥ śilāḥ|
ṛtū śiśirahemantau ājagmaturatidyutī|| 13.92||
tābhyām ṛtubhyāṃ prāptābhyāṃ himavān sa nagottamaḥ|
prāleyacūrṇavarṣibhyāṃ kṣipraṃ raupya ivābabhau|| 13.93||
tena prāleyavarṣeṇa ghanena sa himācalaḥ|
agādhena tadā reje kṣīroda iva sāgaraḥ|| 13.94||
himasthāneṣu himavān nāśayāmāsa pādapān|
sādhūpacārān sahasā kṛtārtha iva durjanaḥ|| 13.95||
prāleyapaṭalacchannaiḥ śṛṅgaiḥ sa śuśubhe nagaḥ|
chatrairiva mahābhogaiḥ pāṇḍaraiḥ pṛthivīpatiḥ|| 13.96||
pāṇḍarāṇi viśālāni śrīmanti subhagāni ca|
tuṅgāni cādriśṛṅgāṇi saudhānīva cakāśire|| 13.97||
tasyācalendrasya darīṣvatīva vicitrasāraṅgakulākulāsu|
prāleyadhārāḥ śaśipādagaurā gokṣīradhārā iva saṃnipetuḥ|| 13.98||
bahukusumarajobhirutkarāṅgā himakaṇasaṅgasuśītalāḥ samīrāḥ|
vavuramaragaṇeśvarāmbarāṇi pratanutamāni śanairvikampayantaḥ|| 13.99||
nirdhūtarūkṣānilaśītadoṣaḥ prodbhinnacūtāṅkurakarṇapūraḥ|
vasantakālaśca tam adriputrīsevārtham āgāddhimavantam āśu|| 13.100||
tasminnṛtāvadrisutāvivāhasiṣevayā taṃ girim abhyupete|
prādurbabhūvuḥ kusumāvataṃsāḥ samantataḥ pādapagulmaṣaṇḍāḥ|| 13.101||
vavuḥ sugandhāḥ subhagāḥ suśītā vicitrapuṣpāgrarajotkarāṅgāḥ|
manobhavodrekakarāḥ surāṇāṃ surāṅganānāṃ ca muhuḥ samīrāḥ|| 13.102||
svacchāmbupūrṇāśca tathā nalinyaḥ padmotpalānāṃ mukulairupetāḥ|
īṣatsamudbhinnapayodharāgrā nāryo yathā ramyatamā babhūvuḥ|| 13.103||
ṛtoḥ svabhāvācca madodbhavācca phullāsu śākhāsu nilīnapakṣāḥ|
cetobhirāmaṃ tridaśāṅganānāṃ puṃskokilāścātikalaṃ vineduḥ|| 13.104||
nātyuṣṇaśītāni saraḥpayāṃsi kiñjalkacūrṇaiḥ kapilīkṛtāni|
cakrāhvayugmairupanāditāni papuḥ prahṛṣṭāḥ suradantimukhyāḥ|| 13.105||
priyaṅgūścūtataravaścūtāṃścāpi priyaṅgavaḥ|
tarjayanta ivānyonyaṃ mañjarībhiścakāśire|| 13.106||
himaśukleṣu śṛṅgeṣu tilakāḥ kusumotkarāḥ|
śuśubhuḥ kāryam uddiśya vṛddhā iva samāgatāḥ|| 13.107||
phullāśokalatāstatra rejire śālasaṃśritāḥ|
kāminya iva kāntānāṃ kaṇṭhālambitamūrtayaḥ|| 13.108||
samadālikulodgītalatākusumasaṃcayāḥ|
parasparaṃ hi mālatyo bhāṣantya iva rejire|| 13.109||
nīlāni nīlāmburuhaiḥ payāṃsi gaurāṇi gauraiśca sanāladaṇḍaiḥ|
raktaiśca raktāni bhṛśaṃ kṛtāni mattadvirephārdhavidaṣṭapatraiḥ|| 13.110||
haimāni vistīrṇajaleṣu keṣucinnirantaraṃ mārakatāni keṣucit|
vaidūryanālāni saraḥsu keṣucit prajajñire padmavanāni sarvataḥ|| 13.111||
vāpyastatrābhavan ramyāḥ kamalotpalabhūṣitāḥ|
nānāvihagasaṃghuṣṭā hemasopānapaṅktayaḥ|| 13.112||
śṛṅgāṇi tasya tu gireḥ karṇikāraiḥ supuṣpitaiḥ|
samucchritānyaviralairhaimānīva babhurmune|| 13.113||
īṣadudbhinnakusumaiḥ pāṭalaiścāpi pāṭalāḥ|
sambabhūvurdiśaḥ sarvāḥ pavanākampimūrtibhiḥ|| 13.114||
kṛṣṇāñjanādriśṛṅgābhā nīlāśokamahīruhāḥ|
girau vavṛdhire phullāḥ spardhayeva parasparam|| 13.115||
cīruvākavighuṣṭāni kiṃśukānāṃ vanāni ca|
parvatasya nitambeṣu sarveṣvevābhijajñire|| 13.116||
tamālagulmaistasyāsīcchobhā himavatastadā|
nīlajīmūtasaṃghātairnilīnairiva sandhiṣu|| 13.117||
nikāmapuṣpaiḥ suviśālaśākhaiḥ samucchritaiścampakapādapaiśca|
pramattapuṃskokilasampralāpairhimācalo 'atīva tadā rarāja|| 13.118||
śrutvā śabdaṃ ṛtumadakalaṃ sarvataḥ kokilānāṃ
paṭusūryātapaścāpi prāyaḥ soṣṇajalāśayaḥ|
devīvivāhasevārthaṃ grīṣma āgāddhimācalam|| 13.120||
sa cāpi tarubhistatra bahubhiḥ kusumotkaraiḥ|
śobhayāmāsa śṛṅgāṇi prāleyādreḥ samantataḥ|| 13.121||
tasyāpi ca ṛtostatra vāyavaḥ sumanoharāḥ|
vavuḥ pāṭalavistīrṇakadambārjunagandhinaḥ|| 13.122||
vāpyaḥ praphullapadmaughāḥ kesarāruṇamūrtayaḥ|
abhavaṃstaṭasaṃghuṣṭakalahaṃsakadambakāḥ|| 13.123||
tathā kuravakāścāpi kusumāpāṇḍumūrtayaḥ|
sarveṣu jajñuḥ śṛṅgeṣu bhramarāvalisevitāḥ|| 13.124||
bakulāśca nitambeṣu viśāleṣu mahībhṛtaḥ|
utsasarjurmanojñāni kusumāni samantataḥ|| 13.125||
iti kusumavicitrasarvavṛkṣā vividhavihaṃgamanādaramyadeśāḥ|
himagiritanayāvivāhabhūtyai ṣaḍupayayurṛtavo munipravīra|| 13.126||
tata evaṃ pravṛtte tu sarvabhūtasamāgame|
nānāvādyaśatākīrṇe brahmā mama pitā svayam|| 13.127||
śailaputrīm alaṃkṛtya yogyābharaṇasampadā|
puraṃ praveśayāmāsa svayam ādāya lokadhṛk|| 13.128||
tatastu punareveśaṃ brahmā vyajñāpayadvibhum|
havirjuhomi vahnau tu upādhyāyapade sthitaḥ|
dadāsi mahyaṃ yadi ājñāṃ kartavyo 'ayaṃ kriyāvidhiḥ|| 13.129||
tam āha śaṃkaro devaṃ devadevo jagatpatiḥ|
yadyadiṣṭaṃ sureśāna tat kuruṣva yathepsitam|
kartāsmi vacanaṃ sarvaṃ brahmaṃstava jagadvibho|| 13.130||
tataḥ praṇamya hṛṣṭātmā brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
hastaṃ devasya devyāśca yogabandhe yuyoja ha|| 13.131||
jvalanaṃ ca svayaṃ kṛtvā kṛtāñjalim upasthitaṃ |
śrutigītairmahāmantrairmūrtimadbhirupasthitaiḥ|| 13.132||
yathoktavidhinā hutvā sarpistadamṛtaṃ ca hi|
triśca taṃ jvalanaṃ devaṃ kārayitvā pradakṣiṇam|| 13.133||
muktvā hastasamāyogaṃ sahitaḥ sarvadevataiḥ|
sutaiśca mānasaiḥ sarvaiḥ prahṛṣṭenāntarātmanā|
vṛtte udvāhakāle tu praṇanāma vṛṣadhvajam|| 13.134||
yogenaiva tayorvyāsa tadomāparameśayoḥ|
udvāhaḥ sa paro vṛtto yaṃ devā na viduḥ kvacit|| 13.135||
iti te sarvam ākhyātaṃ svayaṃvaram idaṃ śubham|
udvāhaścaiva devasya śṛṇvataḥ paramādbhutam|| 13.136||
iti skandapurāṇe
nāma trayodaśo .adhyāyaḥ|| 13.13||

caturdaśamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha vṛtte vivāhe tu bhavasyāmitatejasaḥ|
praharṣam atulaṃ gatvā devāḥ sahapitāmahāḥ|
tuṣṭuvurvāgbhiriṣṭābhiḥ praṇamanto maheśvaram|| 14.1||
namaḥ parvataliṅgāya parvateśāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ pavanavegāya virūpāyājitāya ca|| 14.2||
namaḥ kleśavināśāya dātre ca śubhasampadām|
namo nīlaśikhaṇḍāya ambikāpataye namaḥ|| 14.3||
namaḥ pavanarūpāya śatarūpāya vai namaḥ|
namo bhairavarūpāya virūpanayanāya ca|| 14.4||
namaḥ sahasranetrāya sahasracaraṇāya ca|
namo vedarahasyāya vedāṅgāya namo namaḥ|| 14.5||
viṣṭambhanāya śakrasya bāhorvedāṅkurāya ca|
carācarādhipataye śamanāya namo namaḥ|| 14.6||
salileśayaliṅgāya yugāntāyataliṅgine|
namaḥ kapālamālāya kapālasragmiṇe namaḥ|| 14.7||
namaḥ kapālahastāya daṃṣṭriṇe gadine namaḥ|
namastrailokyavāhāya saptalokarathāya ca|| 14.8||
namaḥ khaṭvāṅgahastāya pramathārtiharāya ca|
namo yajñaśirohartre kṛṣṇakeśāpahāriṇe|| 14.9||
bhaganetranipātāya pūṣṇo dantaharāya ca|
namaḥ pinākaśūlāsikhaḍgamudgaradhāriṇe|| 14.10||
suvarṇaretase caiva sarpakuṇḍaladhāriṇe|
vāḍvaleryoganāśāya yogināṃ gurave namaḥ|| 14.12||
śaśāṅkādityanetrāya lalāṭanayanāya ca|
namaḥ śmaśānarataye śmaśānavaradāya ca|| 14.13||
namo daivatanāthāya tryambakāya namo namaḥ|
aśanīśatahāsāya brahmaṇyāyājitāya ca|| 14.14||
gṛhasthasādhave nityaṃ jaṭine brahmacāriṇe|
namo muṇḍārdhamuṇḍāya paśūnāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 14.15||
salile tapyamānāya yogaiśvaryapradāya ca|
namaḥ śāntāya dāntāya pralayotpattikāriṇe|| 14.16||
namo 'anugrahakartre ca sthitikartre namo namaḥ|
namo rudrāya vasave ādityāyāśvine namaḥ|| 14.17||
namaḥ pitre 'atha sādhyāya viśvedevāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ śarvāya sarvāya ugrāya varadāya ca|| 14.18||
namo bhīmāya senānye paśūnāṃ pataye namaḥ|
śucaye rerihāṇāya sadyojātāya vai namaḥ|| 14.19||
mahādevāya citrāya namaścitrarathāya ca|
pradhānāya prameyāya kāryāya karaṇāya ca|| 14.20||
puruṣāya namaste 'astu puruṣecchākarāya ca|
namaḥ puruṣasaṃyogapradhānaguṇakāriṇe|| 14.21||
pravartakāya prakṛteḥ puruṣasya ca sarvaśaḥ|
kṛtākṛtasya saṃvettre phalasaṃyogadāya ca|| 14.22||
kālajñāya ca sarvatra namo niyamakāriṇe|
namo vaiṣamyakartre ca guṇānāṃ vṛttidāya ca|| 14.23||
namaste devadeveśa namaste bhūtabhāvana|
śivaḥ saumyaḥ sukho draṣṭuṃ bhava somo hi naḥ prabho|| 14.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa bhagavān devo jagatpatirumāpatiḥ|
stūyamānaḥ suraiḥ sarvairamarānidam abravīt|| 14.25||
draṣṭuṃ sukhaśca saumyaśca devānām asmi bho surāḥ|
varaṃ brūta yatheṣṭaṃ ca dātāsmi vadatānaghāḥ|| 14.26||
tataste praṇatāḥ sarve ūcuḥ sabrahmakāḥ surāḥ|
tavaiva bhagavan haste vara eṣo 'avatiṣṭhatām|
yadā kāryaṃ tadā nastvaṃ dāsyase varam īpsitam|| 14.27||
evam astviti tānuktvā visṛjya ca surān haraḥ|
lokāṃśca pramathaiḥ sārdhaṃ viveśa bhavanaṃ tataḥ|| 14.28||
yastu harotsavam adbhutam etaṃ gāyati daivataviprasamakṣam|
so 'apratirūpagaṇeśasamāno dehaviparyayam etya sukhī syāt|| 14.29||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
pārāśarya stavaṃ hīdaṃ śṛṇuyādyaḥ paṭheta vā|
sa svargalokago devaiḥ pūjyate 'amararāḍiva|| 14.30||
iti skandapurāṇe caturdaśamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 14.14||

pañcadaśamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
praviṣṭe bhavanaṃ deve sūpaviṣṭe varāsane|
sa bahirmanmathaḥ krūro devaṃ veddhumanābhavat|| 15.1||
tam anācārasaṃyuktaṃ durātmānaṃ kulādhamam|
lokān sarvāṃstāpayānaṃ sarveṣvakaruṇātmakam|| 15.2||
ṛṣīṇāṃ vighnakartāraṃ niyamānāṃ vrataiḥ saha|
cakrāhvayasya rūpeṇa ratyā saha tam āgatam|| 15.3||
athātatāyinaṃ vyāsa veddhukāmaṃ sureśvaram|
nayanena tṛtīyena sāvajñaṃ tam avaikṣata|| 15.4||
tato 'asya netrajo vahnirjvālāmālāsahasravān|
saṃvṛtya ratibhartāram adahat saparicchadam|| 15.5||
sa dahyamānaḥ karuṇam ārto 'akrośata visvaram|
prasādayaṃśca taṃ devaṃ papāta sa mahītale|| 15.6||
āśu so 'agniparītāṅgo manmatho lokatāpanaḥ|
papāta bhasmasāccaiva kṣaṇena samapadyata|| 15.7||
patnī tu karuṇaṃ tasya vilalāpa suduḥkhitā|
devaṃ devīṃ ca duḥkhārtā ayācat karuṇāyatī|| 15.8||
tasyāśca karuṇāṃ śrutvā devau tau karuṇātmakau|
ūcatustāṃ samālokya samāśvāsya ca duḥkhitām|| 15.9||
dagdha eṣa dhruvaṃ bhadre nāsyotpattiriheṣyate|
aśarīro 'api te kāle kāryaṃ sarvaṃ kariṣyati|| 15.10||
yadā tu viṣṇurbhavitā vasudevasutaḥ śubhe|
tadā tasya suto 'ayaṃ syāt patiste sa bhaviṣyati|| 15.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sā taṃ varaṃ labdhvā kāmapatnī śubhānanā|
jagāmeṣṭaṃ tadā deśaṃ prītiyuktā gataklamā|| 15.12||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ dagdhvā sa kāmaṃ tu śaṃkaro mūḍhacetasam|
provāca himavatputrīṃ bhaktyā munivarasya ha|| 15.13||
vasiṣṭho nāma viprendro māṃ kṛtvā hṛdi tapyate|
tasyāhaṃ varadānāya prayāsyāmi mahāvrate|| 15.14||
evam uktvā sa devīṃ tu bhaktiprītyā tadā vibhuḥ|
jagāma tapyato 'abhyāśaṃ vasiṣṭhasya munervibhuḥ|| 15.15||
tato munivaraśreṣṭhaṃ variṣṭhaṃ tapatāṃ varam|
vasiṣṭham ṛṣiśārdūlaṃ tapyamānaṃ paraṃ tapaḥ|| 15.16||
pūrṇe varṣasahasre tu jvalamānam ivānalam|
uvāca bhagavān gatvā brūhi kiṃ te dadāni te|
dadāmi divyaṃ cakṣuste paśya māṃ sagaṇaṃ dvija|| 15.17||
dṛṣṭvā sa tu tam īśānaṃ praṇamya śirasā prabhum|
śirasyañjalim ādhāya tuṣṭāva hṛṣitānanaḥ|| 15.18||
vasiṣṭha uvāca|
namaḥ kanakaliṅgāya vedaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ sahasraliṅgāya vahniliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.19||
namaḥ purāṇaliṅgāya śrutiliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ pavanaliṅgāya brahmaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.20||
namastrailokyaliṅgāya dāhaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ parvataliṅgāya sthitiliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.21||
namo rahasyaliṅgāya saptadvīpordhvaliṅgine|
namaḥ sarvārthaliṅgāya sarvalokāṅgaliṅgine|| 15.22||
namo 'astvavyaktaliṅgāya buddhiliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namo 'ahaṃkāraliṅgāya bhūtaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.23||
nama indriyaliṅgāya namastanmātraliṅgine|
namaḥ puruṣaliṅgāya bhāvaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.24||
namaḥ sarvārthaliṅgāya tamoliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namo rajordhvaliṅgāya sattvaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.25||
namo gaganaliṅgāya tejoliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namo vāyūrdhvaliṅgāya śabdaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.26||
namo ṛkstutaliṅgāya yajurliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namaste 'atharvaliṅgāya sāmaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 15.27||
namo yajñāṅgaliṅgāya yajñaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|
namaste 'anantaliṅgāya devānugataliṅgine|| 15.28||
diśa naḥ paramaṃ yogam apatyaṃ matsamaṃ tathā|
brahma caivākṣayaṃ deva śamaṃ caiva paraṃ vibho|
akṣayatvaṃ ca vaṃśasya dharme ca matim akṣayām|| 15.29||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa bhagavān vyāsa vasiṣṭhenāmitātmanā|
stūyamānastutoṣātha tuṣṭaścedaṃ tam abravīt|| 15.30||
bhagavānuvāca|
tuṣṭaste 'ahaṃ dadānyetat tava sarvaṃ manogatam|
yogaṃ ca paramaṃ sūkṣmam akṣayaṃ sarvakāmikam|| 15.31||
pautraṃ ca tvatsamaṃ divyaṃ tapoyogabalānvitam|
dadāni te ṛṣiśreṣṭha pratibhāsyanti caiva te|| 15.32||
damaḥ śamastathā kīrtistuṣṭirakrodha eva ca|
nityaṃ tava bhaviṣyanti amaratvaṃ ca sarvaśaḥ|| 15.33||
avadhyatvam asahyatvam akṣayatvaṃ ca sarvadā|
vaṃśasya cākṣatirvipra dharme ca ratiravyayā|
brūhi cānyānapi varān dadāmi ṛṣisattama|| 15.34||
vasiṣṭha uvāca|
bhagavan viditaṃ sarvaṃ bhaviṣyaṃ devasattama|
na syāddhi tat tathā deva yathā vā manyase prabho|| 15.35||
tathā tannātra saṃdeho vihitaṃ yadyathā mayā|
tasmāt te 'anugrahaṃ kartā bhūyaḥ putrastavāvyayaḥ|| 15.37||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā tato devaḥ kapardī nīlalohitaḥ|
paśyatastasya viprarṣeḥ kṣaṇādantaradhīyata|| 15.38||
iti skandapurāṇe pañcadaśamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 15.15||

ṣoḍaśo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
varān sa labdhvā bhagavān vasiṣṭho 'asmatpitāmahaḥ|
kaṃ putraṃ janayāmāsa ātmanaḥ sadṛśadyutim|| 16.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tenāsau varadānena devadevasya śūlinaḥ|
arundhatyām ajanayat tapoyogabalānvitam|
brahmiṣṭhaṃ śaktināmānaṃ putraṃ putraśatāgrajam|| 16.2||
tasya bālyāt prabhṛtyeva vāsiṣṭhasya mahātmanaḥ|
pareṇa cetasā bhaktirabhavadgovṛṣadhvaje|| 16.3||
sa kadācidapatyārtham ārādhayadumāpatim|
tasya tuṣṭo mahādevo varado 'asmītyabhāṣata|| 16.4||
atha dṛṣṭvā tam īśānam idam āhānatānanaḥ|
kena stoṣyāmi te deva yastvaṃ sarvajagatpatiḥ|
sarvān dhārayase lokān ātmanā samayādvibho|| 16.5||
tvam eva bhoktā bhojyaṃ ca kartā kāryaṃ tathā kriyā|
utpādakastathotpādya utpattiścaiva sarvaśaḥ|| 16.6||
ātmānaṃ putranāmānaṃ mama tulyaṃ guṇairvibho|
icchāmi dattaṃ deveśa eṣa me dīyatāṃ varaḥ|| 16.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tam evaṃvādinaṃ devaḥ prahasya vadatāṃ varaḥ|
uvāca vacasā vyāsa diśaḥ sarvā vinādayan|| 16.8||
tvayāhaṃ yācitaḥ śakte sa ca te saṃbhaviṣyati|
tvatsamaḥ sarvavedajñastvadīyo munipuṃgava|| 16.9||
bījātmā ca tathodbhūtaḥ svayam evāṅkurātmanā|
bījātmanā na bhavati pariṇāmāntaraṃ gataḥ|| 16.10||
evaṃ sa ātmanātmā vaḥ saṃbhūto 'apatyasaṃjñitaḥ|
svenātmanā na bhavitā pariṇāmāntaraṃ gataḥ|| 16.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā tu taṃ devaḥ prahasya ca nirīkṣya ca|
jagāma sahasā yogī adṛśyatvam atidyutiḥ|| 16.12||
tasmin gate mahādeve śaktistava pitāmahaḥ|
vacastat pariniścintya evam evetyamanyata|| 16.13||
atha kāle 'atimahati samatīte śubhavrate|
tapasā bhāvitaścāpi mahatāgnisamaprabhaḥ|
adṛśyantyāṃ mahāprajña ādadhe garbham uttamam|| 16.14||
tasyām āpannasattvāyāṃ rājā kalmāṣapādṛṣim|
bhakṣayāmāsa saṃrabdho rakṣasā hṛtacetanaḥ|| 16.15||
iti skandapurāṇe ṣoḍaśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 16.16||

saptadaśo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
kasmāt sa rājā tam ṛṣiṃ cakhāda tapasānvitam|
rakṣasā sa kim arthaṃ ca hṛtacetābhavannṛpaḥ|| 17.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vasiṣṭhayājyo rājāsīnnāmnā mitrasahaḥ prabhuḥ|
sudāsaputro balavānindracandrasamadyutiḥ|| 17.2||
tam āgamyocivāñchaktiścariṣye dīkṣito vratam|
tatra me niśi rājendra sadaiva piśitāśanam|| 17.3||
ihāgatasya yacchasva śuci sarvaguṇānvitam|
apratīkārasaṃyuktam ekadaikānta eva ca|| 17.4||
evam astviti tenokto jagāma sa mahāmanāḥ|
athāsyāntarhitaṃ rakṣo nṛpaterabhavat tadā|
nājñāpayat tadā sūdaṃ tasyārthe munisattama|| 17.5||
gate 'atha divase tāta saṃsmṛtya prayatātmavān|
sūdam āhūya covāca ārtavat sa narādhipaḥ|| 17.6||
saudāsa uvāca|
mayāmṛtavaso prātarguruputrasya dhīmataḥ|
piśitaṃ sampratijñātaṃ bhojanaṃ niśi saṃskṛtam|
tat kuruṣva tathā kṣipraṃ kālo no nātyagādyathā|| 17.7||
sa evam uktaḥ provāca sūdo 'amṛtavasustadā|
rājaṃstvayā no nākhyātaṃ prāgeva narapuṃgava|
sāmprataṃ nāsti piśitaṃ stokam apyabhikāṅkṣitam|| 17.8||
piśitasyaiva cālpatvādbahūnāṃ caiva tadbhujām|
amitasya pradānācca na kiṃcidavaśiṣyate|| 17.9||
rājovāca|
jāne sarvopayogaṃ ca jāne cāduṣṭatāṃ tava|
jāne stokaṃ ca piśitaṃ kāryaṃ cedaṃ tathāvidham|
mṛgyatāṃ piśitaṃ kṣipraṃ labdhavyaṃ yatra manyase|| 17.10||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam ukto 'amṛtavasuḥ prayatnaṃ mahadāsthitaḥ|
piśitaṃ mṛgayan samyaṅnāpyavindata karhicit|| 17.11||
yadā na labdhavān māṃsaṃ tadovāca narādhipam|
gatvā niśi mahārājam idaṃ vacanam arthavat|| 17.12||
rājan na piśitaṃ tvasti pure 'asmiñchuci karhicit|
mṛgayan parikhinno 'asmi śādhi kiṃ karavāṇi te|| 17.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktaḥ sūdena tasmin kāle narādhipaḥ|
novāca kiṃcit taṃ sūdaṃ tūṣṇīm eva babhūva ha|| 17.14||
tadantaram abhiprekṣya viśvāmitrasamīritaḥ|
rākṣaso rudhiro nāma saṃviveśa narādhipam|| 17.15||
rakṣasā sa tadāviṣṭo rudhireṇa durātmanā|
uvāca sūdaṃ śanakaiḥ karṇamūle mahādyutiḥ|| 17.16||
gaccha yat kiṃcidānīya māṃsaṃ mānuṣam antataḥ|
gārdabhaṃ vāpyathauṣṭraṃ vā sarvaṃ saṃskartum arhasi|| 17.17||
kim asau jñāsyate rātrau tvayā bhūyaśca saṃskṛtam|
rasavadgandhavaccaiva kṣipram eva samācara|| 17.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktastenātha mānuṣaṃ māṃsam ādade|
rājāpakāriṇo vyāsa mṛtotsṛṣṭasya kasyacit|| 17.19||
athārdharātrasamaye bhāskarākāravarcasam|
śatānalasamaprakhyam apaśyanmunisattamam|| 17.20||
sa tam arghyeṇa pādyena āsanāgryavareṇa ca|
samarcayitvā vidhivadannam asyopapādayat|| 17.21||
sa tadannaṃ samānītaṃ samālabhya mahātapāḥ|
cukopa kupitaścāha pārthivaṃ pradahanniva|| 17.22||
śaktiruvāca|
pārthivādhama viprāṇāṃ bhojanaṃ rākṣasocitam|
na dīyate vidhijñena tvaṃ tu mām avamanyase|| 17.23||
yasmāt tvaṃ rākṣasam idaṃ mahyaṃ ditsasi bhojanam|
tasmāt tvaṃ karmaṇā tena puruṣādo bhaviṣyasi|| 17.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktastu tejasvī rājā saṃcintya tat tadā|
uvāca krodharaktākṣo rākṣasāviṣṭacetanaḥ|| 17.25||
puruṣādo bhavetyevaṃ mām avocadbhavān yataḥ|
tatastvāṃ bhakṣayiṣyāmi bhrātṛbhiḥ sahitaṃ dvija|| 17.26||
bhakṣayitvā viśuddhyarthaṃ muktaśāpastataḥ param|
cariṣyāmi tapaḥ śuddhaṃ saṃyamyendriyasaṃhatim|
pitrā tavābhyanujñātaḥ svarge vatsye yathepsitam|| 17.27||
iti skandapurāṇe
saptadaśamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 17.17||

aṣṭādaśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa rājā svaṃ rājyam utsṛjya saha bhāryayā|
vanaṃ viveśa tatrābhūt puruṣādo mahābalaḥ|| 18.1||
so 'abhakṣayata tatrāgre śaktim eva mahāmunim|
tato bhrātṛśataṃ tasya vasiṣṭhasyaiva paśyataḥ|| 18.2||
tataḥ putravadhaṃ ghoraṃ dṛṣṭvā brahmasutaḥ prabhuḥ|
notsasarja tadā krodhaṃ vasiṣṭhaḥ kauśikaṃ prati|
putraśokena mahatā bhṛśam evānvakīryata|| 18.3||
sa baddhvā mahatīṃ kaṇṭhe śilāṃ brahmasutaḥ prabhuḥ|
nadyām ātmānam utsṛjya śatadhā sādravadbhayāt|
śatadrūriti tāṃ prāhurmunayaḥ saṃśitavratāḥ|| 18.4||
punaḥ pāśairdṛḍhairbaddhvā anyasyām asṛjadvaśī|
tasyāṃ vipāśaḥ saṃvṛtto vipāśā sābhavat tataḥ|| 18.5||
tato 'aṭavīṃ samāsādya nirāhāro jitendriyaḥ|
vāyubhakṣastadā tasthau svaṃ dehaṃ paritāpayan|| 18.6||
atha śuśrāva vedānāṃ dhvanim ekasya susvaram|
adhīyānasya tatrāśu dhyānam evānvapadyata|| 18.7||
athainaṃ cārusarvāṅgī pīnonnatapayodharā|
upatasthe 'agrataḥ patnī śakterdīnānanekṣaṇā|| 18.8||
tām uvāca kutastvaṃ vai kasyaiṣa śrūyate dhvaniḥ|
sovāca dīnayā vācā rudatī śvaśuraṃ tadā|| 18.9||
adṛśyantyuvāca|
yadaiva sutaduḥkhena nirgato 'asi āśramādguro|
tadāprabhṛtyevādṛśyā bhagavantam anuvratā|| 18.10||
adhīyānasya caivāyaṃ dhvaniḥ putrasya te vibho|
udarasthasya te sūnormā duḥkhe tvaṃ manaḥ kṛthāḥ|| 18.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
idānīm asti me vatse jīvitāśeti so 'abravīt|
kṣāntiṃ dhṛtiṃ ca saṃsthitya prayayau āśramaṃ muniḥ|| 18.12||
tadāśramapadaṃ gacchan pathi rājānam aikṣata|
vasārudhiradigdhāṅgaṃ saudāsaṃ raktalocanam|| 18.13||
abhidravantaṃ vegena mantrairastambhayanmuniḥ|
tato 'asya nirgataḥ kāyādrakṣaḥ paramadāruṇaḥ|| 18.14||
uvāca cainaṃ duṣṭātman daheyaṃ tvāṃ sabāndhavam|
dagdhena ca tvayā kiṃ me gaccha mukto 'asi durmate|| 18.15||
tataḥ sa mukto dīnātmā rākṣasaḥ krūrakarmakṛt|
praṇamya śirasā bhīto jagāma kuśikāntikam|| 18.16||
gate niśācare rājā praṇamya śirasā munim|
prasādayāmāsa tadā sa covācedam arthavat|| 18.17||
na doṣastava rājendra rakṣasādhiṣṭhitasya vai|
kṛtāntena hatāḥ putrā nimittaṃ tatra rākṣasaḥ|| 18.18||
praśādhi rājyaṃ rājendra pitṛpaitāmahaṃ vibho|
brūhi kiṃ vā priyaṃ te 'adya karomi narapuṃgava|| 18.19||
rājovāca|
icchāmi bhagavan putraṃ tvayotpāditam acyuta|
devyām asyāṃ mahāsattvaṃ tat kuruṣva mama priyam|| 18.20||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam astvityathoktvāsau tasyāṃ patnyāṃ mahāvrataḥ|
putraṃ ca śoṇakaṃ nāma janayāmāsa nirvṛtaḥ|| 18.21||
taṃ śoṇakaṃ tato rājye svaṃ putram abhiṣicya saḥ|
jagāma vanam evāśu sabhāryastapasi sthitaḥ|| 18.22||
vasiṣṭhasyāpi kālena śakteḥ putraḥ pratāpavān|
adṛśyantyāṃ samabhavat putro nāmnā parāśaraḥ|| 18.23||
vasiṣṭhaṃ tu tadā dhīmāṃstātam evābhyamanyata|
tāta tāteti ca muhurvyājahāra piturgurum|| 18.24||
tataḥ kadācidvijñāya bhakṣitaṃ rakṣasā śucim|
pitaraṃ tapasā mantrairīje rakṣaḥkratau tadā|| 18.25||
tatra koṭīḥ sa pañcāśadrakṣasāṃ krūrakarmaṇām|
juhāvāgnau mahātejāstato brahmābhyagāddrutam|| 18.26||
sutam abhyetya sampūjya vasiṣṭhasahitaḥ prabhuḥ|
ṛṣibhirdaivataiścaiva idam āha parāśaram|| 18.27||
brahmovāca|
aṣṭamaṃ sthānam etaddhi devānām ādyam īdṛśam\dagnote|| 18.28||
parāśara uvāca|
saha devairahaṃ sarvā/llokān dhakṣyāmi pāvakaiḥ|
dagdhvānyān prathayiṣyāmi tatra lokān na saṃśayaḥ|| 18.29||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyaivaṃ garvitaṃ vākyaṃ śrutvā devaḥ pitāmahaḥ|
uvāca ślakṣṇayā vācā sāntvayaṃstam idaṃ vacaḥ|| 18.30||
pitāmaha uvāca|
kṛtam etanna saṃdeho yathā brūṣe mahāmate|
kṣantavyaṃ sarvam etat tu asmatpriyacikīrṣayā|| 18.31||
yaiste pitā mahābhāga bhakṣitaḥ saha sodaraiḥ|
ta evāgnau ca hotavyā viśvāmitrasya paśyataḥ|
anyeṣāṃ svasti sarvatra devānāṃ saha rākṣasaiḥ|| 18.32||
vasiṣṭhasya mahābhāga tvaṃ nivāraya putraka\dagnote|| 18.33||
}$\versenum=33$
devāḥ prāñjalayaḥ sarve praṇemuste mahāmunim|
ṛṣayaścaiva te sarve vāgbhistuṣṭuvire tadā|| 18.34||
tatasteṣāṃ mahātejā vacāṃsi pratyapūjayat|
viśvāmitrasya miṣata idaṃ provāca susvaram|| 18.35||
ya eṣāṃ brāhmaṇo vāpi kṣatriyo vā durātmavān|
rakṣasāṃ pakṣam āsthāya pratīkāraṃ kariṣyati|| 18.36||
tam apyatrāpi saṃkruddhastapoyogabalānvitaḥ|
vihatya tapaso yogāddhoṣye dīpte vibhāvasau|| 18.37||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato devāḥ sagandharvāḥ pitāmahapuraḥsarāḥ|
prabhāvaṃ tasya taṃ jñātvā parāśaram apūjayan|| 18.38||
huteṣu ca tatasteṣu rākṣaseṣu durātmasu|
saṃjahāra tataḥ sattraṃ brahmaṇo 'anumate tadā|| 18.39||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ śrāddhakāle vā daive karmaṇi vā dvijān|
śrāvayīta śucirbhūtvā na taṃ hiṃsanti rākṣasāḥ|| 18.40||
parāśarasyedam adīnasambhavaṃ viśuddhavākkarmavidhānasambhavam|
niśāmya vipraḥ kulasiddhisambhavaṃ na rākṣasaṃ gacchati yonisambhavam|| 18.41||
iti skandapurāṇe 'aṣṭādaśamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 18.18||

ūnaviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ tava pitā vyāsa rakṣaḥsattraṃ samāharat|
samāpayitvā ca punastapastepe ca bhāsvaram|| 19.1||
tam āgatya vasiṣṭhastu tapasā bhāskaradyutim|
uvāca prītisampannam idam arthavadavyayaḥ|| 19.2||
vasiṣṭha uvāca|
pitaraḥ putrakāmā vai tapaḥ kṛtvātiduścaram|
putram utpādayanti sma tapojñānasamanvitam|| 19.3||
ayaṃ naḥ saṃtatiṃ caiva jñānavāṃstapasānvitaḥ|
kariṣyati gatiṃ caiva iti vedavido viduḥ|| 19.4||
sa tvaṃ taponvitaścaiva jñānavān yaśasānvitaḥ|
putraḥ putravatāṃ śreṣṭho vihīnaḥ prajayā vibho|| 19.5||
tasmāt pitR̥ṇām ānṛṇyaṃ gaccha vratavatāṃ vara|
sutam utpādaya kṣipram adhikaṃ samam eva vā|| 19.6||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktastejasvī vasiṣṭhenāmitātmanā|
mainākaṃ parvataṃ prāpya tapastepe suduścaram|| 19.7||
tasya kālena mahatā tapasā bhāvitasya tu|
umāpatirvaraṃ prādāt sa ca vavre sutaṃ śubham|| 19.8||
sa labdhavara āgamya yayāce putrakāraṇāt|
kṣetraṃ supariśuddhaṃ ca svaputro yatra sambhavet|| 19.9||
sambhraman dāśarājasya duhitṛtvam upāgatām|
pitṛkanyāṃ tataḥ kālīm apaśyaddivyarūpiṇīm|| 19.10||
matsīgarbhasamutpannāṃ vasorbījāśanāt purā|
adrikām apsaraḥśreṣṭhāṃ brahmatejomayīṃ śubhām|| 19.11||
tasyāṃ sa janayāmāsa varaṃ dattvā mahātapāḥ|
bhavantaṃ tapasāṃ yoniṃ śrautasmārtapravartakam|| 19.12||
tava putro 'abhavaccāpi śuko yogavidāṃ varaḥ|
tasya putrāśca catvāraḥ kanyā caikā sumadhyamā|| 19.13||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ vairaṃ samabhavadviśvāmitravasiṣṭhayoḥ|
kathaṃ cāpagataṃ bhūya etadicchāmi veditum|| 19.14||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
parāśare tu garbhasthe vipratvaṃ gādhije gate|
sarasvatyāṃ kurukṣetre dvayorapi āśramau tayoḥ|| 19.15||
tatra vairam anusmṛtya viśvāmitreṇa dhīmatā|
miṣatastu vasiṣṭhasya hataṃ putraśataṃ ruṣā|| 19.16||
munirapi āha tatrāsau viśvāmitraḥ pratāpavān|
sarasvatīm athaikānte vasiṣṭhaṃ me mahāpage|
srotasā mahatākṣipya snāyamānam ihānaya|| 19.17||
saivam uktā tu taṃ gatvā vasiṣṭhaṃ prāha duḥkhitā|
yaduktavāṃstu gādheyaḥ sa covāca mahānadīm|| 19.18||
evaṃ kuru mahābhāge māṃ nayasva yathepsitam|
mā te krūraḥ sa gādheyaḥ śāpaṃ dadyāt sudustaram|| 19.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
gādheyasya tataḥ sā tu juhvato 'agniṃ divākare|
madhyaṃ prāpte 'anayadvegādvasiṣṭhaṃ srotasā śubhā|| 19.20||
taṃ dṛṣṭvāpahṛtaṃ vyāsa srotasā munisattamam|
uvāca cchadmanā yasmādvegenāpahṛtastvayā|
tasmāt tvaṃ karmaṇānena sāsṛktoyā bhaviṣyasi|| 19.21||
viśvāmitreṇa sā śaptā nadī lokasukhapradā|
avahadrudhiraṃ caiva māṃsamedastathaiva ca|| 19.22||
atha tīrthaprasaṅgena munibhiḥ samupāgataiḥ|
anugrahaḥ kṛtastasyā yena svacchajalābhavat|| 19.23||
mahatastapasaḥ śaktyā kālena mahatā tadā|
vasiṣṭhasya ca tāṃ kṣāntiṃ jñātvā sa ṛṣipuṃgavaḥ|| 19.24||
viśvāmitro mahātejā vasiṣṭhe vairam atyajat|
evaṃ tau vairam anyonyaṃ jahaturmunisattamau|| 19.25||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyānnityaṃ brāhmaṇāñchrāvayīta vā|
sa dustarāṇi durgāṇi taratyaśrāntapauruṣaḥ|| 19.26||
hrīpauruṣaudāryavihārasattvaiḥ samanvitaḥ sojjvalacāruveṣaḥ|
bhavecca sarvāmararājatulyastripiṣṭape krīḍati cecchayā svayam|| 19.27||
evaṃ tadabhavadvyāsa viśvāmitravasiṣṭhayoḥ|
vairaṃ samāptaṃ lokānāṃ hitārthaṃ punareva ca|| 19.28||
iti skandapurāṇe ūnaviṃśatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 19.19||
viśvāmitrastato gatvā devānām adhipaṃ tadā|
uvāca vajraṃ me dehi śarīraṃ caiva kauśikaḥ|
durvṛttaṃ ca haniṣyāmi vasiṣṭhaṃ brāhmaṇādhamam|| 19.23||
putrāḥ śakra mayā tasya nihatāḥ pāpacetasaḥ|
tān hatvāpi na me śāntirbhavitrī caiva devapa|| 19.24||
śakra uvāca|
brahmeśānau vasiṣṭhaśca tvaṃ caiva munisattama|
nirviśeṣo hi me teṣāṃ na jāne vo hi ceṣṭitam|| 19.25||
sa tatra samabhikruddho gādheyaḥ śakram ojasā|
yogāt pracyāvayāmāsa śarīrāt kālinandana|| 19.26||
sa taccharīram āviśya vṛtraśatroḥ pratāpavān|
vajrodyatakaro bhūtvā chidrānveṣīva tiṣṭhata|| 19.27||
juhvantaṃ sa tam agniṃ tu vajreṇa śataparvaṇā|
ciccheda saptadhā kṛtvā munīnām eva paśyatām|| 19.28||
khaṇḍānyatha samānīya kṣipram eva muniḥ svayam|
saṃdhāya svaṃ śarīraṃ vai sakrodho vākyam abravīt|| 19.29||
tiṣṭha kauśika nedānīṃ mayādṛṣṭo gamiṣyasi|
jānāmi tvām indravākyācchadmanādhiṣṭhitaṃ divi|| 19.30||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktaḥ sa kāleya tejasvī gādhinandanaḥ|
tataḥ sa gagane tasthāvindrarūpī ruṣānvitaḥ|| 19.31||
atha bhāgyāni devānāṃ pranaśyanti mahātmanām|
divākarāt kabandhābhāt peturulkāḥ sahasraśaḥ|| 19.32||
}aśmano rudhiraṃ caiva gaganācca papāta ha|
vavuścāpyaśivā vātā vimānānyapatan divaḥ|
}neśurvedāśca viprāṇāṃ nāgāścākāśagāstathā|| 19.33||
evam ādīṃstathotpātān vividhā/llokanāśakān|
dṛṣṭvā devāḥ samunayastam āhurgādhinandanam|| 19.34||
vasiṣṭhaśca mahātejāstvaṃ ca gādheya dhārmika|
amarau jarayā tyaktau tapoyogabalānvitau|| 19.35||
yuvayorhi kṣayaṃ nāsti kṣayaṃ ca na kariṣyathaḥ|
devatānāṃ salokānāṃ yudhyamānau parasparam|| 19.36||
mattayorgajayoryadvadaraṇye yudhyamānayoḥ|
vīrudhāṃ bhūruhāṃ caiva sambhavatyanayo mahān|| 19.37||
tathā vaireṇa yuvayoḥ pravṛttena mahātmanoḥ|
lokānām anayo vyaktaṃ bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|| 19.38||
tasmādvināśaṃ lokānāṃ devānām ṛṣibhiḥ saha|
yuvayorastu sakhyaṃ ca kṣayo vairasya cāsya vai|| 19.39||
sa evam ukto gādheyo munibhirdaivataiḥ saha|
evam astviti tān prāha vismitastejasā tadā|| 19.40||
tato vasiṣṭham apyevam ūcuḥ sarve divaukasaḥ|
asāvapi tathaiveti ulkāsakhyaṃ cakāra ha|| 19.41||
tataḥprabhṛti sarvaṃ vai jagat sthāvarajaṅgamam|
sasukhaṃ prītiyuktaṃ ca mumude vigatajvaram|| 19.42||
sanatkumāra uvāca|

viṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
umāharau tu deveśau cakraturyacca saṃgatau|
tanme sarvam aśeṣeṇa kathayasva mahāmune|| 20.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
umāharau tu saṃgamya parasparam aninditau|
śālaṅkasyānvaye vipraṃ yuyujāte vareṇa ha|| 20.2||
sa cāpyayonijaḥ putra ārādhya parameśvaram|
rudreṇa samatāṃ labdhvā mahāgaṇapatirbabhau|| 20.3||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ nandī samutpannaḥ kathaṃ cārādhya śaṃkaram|
samānatvam agācchambhoḥ pratīhāratvam eva ca|| 20.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
abhūdṛṣiḥ sa dharmātmā śilādo nāma vīryavān|
tasyābhūcchilakairvṛttiḥ śilādastena so 'abhavat|| 20.5||
apaśyallambamānāṃstu gartāyāṃ sa pitR̥n dvijaḥ|
vicchinnasaṃtatīn ghoraṃ nirayaṃ vai prapetuṣaḥ|| 20.6||
tairukto 'apatyakāmaistu devaṃ lokeśam avyayam|
ārādhaya mahādevaṃ sutārthaṃ dvijasattama|| 20.7||
tasya varṣasahasreṇa tapyamānasya śūladhṛk|
śarvaḥ somo gaṇavṛto varado 'asmītyabhāṣata|| 20.8||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā somam īśeśaṃ praṇataḥ pādayorvibhoḥ|
harṣagadgadayā vācā tuṣṭāva vibudheśvaram|| 20.9||
namaḥ paramadevāya maheśāya mahātmane|
sraṣṭre sarvasureśānāṃ brahmaṇaḥ pataye namaḥ|| 20.10||
namaḥ kāmāṅganāśāya yogasambhavahetave|
namaḥ parvatavāsāya dhyānagamyāya vedhase|| 20.11||
ṛṣīṇāṃ pataye nityaṃ devānāṃ pataye namaḥ|
vedānāṃ pataye caiva yogināṃ pataye namaḥ|| 20.12||
pradhānāya namo nityaṃ tattvāyāmarasaṃjñiṇe|
varadāya ca bhaktānāṃ namaḥ sarvagatāya ca|| 20.13||
tanmātrendriyabhūtānāṃ vikārāṇāṃ guṇaiḥ saha|
sraṣṭre ca pataye caiva namaśca prabhaviṣṇave|| 20.14||
jagataḥ pataye caiva jagatsraṣṭre namaḥ sadā|
prakṛteḥ pataye nityaṃ puruṣāt paragāmine|| 20.15||
śaraṇyāya namo nityaṃ namo bhasmāṅgarāgiṇe|
namaste 'ayograhastāya tejasāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 20.17||
sūryānilahutāśāmbucandrākāśadharāya ca|
sthitāya sarvadā nityaṃ namastrailokavedhase|| 20.18||
stotavyasya kuto deva viśrāmastava vidyate|
yadā hetustvam evāsya jagataḥ sthitināśayoḥ|| 20.19||
aśaraṇyasya deveśa tvattaśca śaraṇārthinaḥ|
prasādaṃ param ālambya varado bhava viśvakṛt|| 20.20||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
yaḥ stotram etadakhilaṃ paṭhate dvijanmā prātaḥ śucirniyamavān purato dvijānām|
taṃ brahmarākṣasaniśācarabhūtayakṣā hiṃsanti no dvipadapannagapūtanāśca|| 20.21||
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaḥ stūyamānaḥ sahomayā|
uvāca varado 'asmīti brūhi yat te manogatam|| 20.22||
tam evaṃvādinaṃ devaṃ śilādo 'abhyarcayat tadā|
uvāca cedaṃ deveśaṃ sa vācā sajjamānayā|| 20.23||
bhagavan yadi tuṣṭo 'asi yadi deyo varaśca me|
icchāmi ātmasamaṃ putraṃ mṛtyuhīnam ayonijam|| 20.24||
evam uktastato devaḥ prīyamāṇastrilocanaḥ|
evam astviti taṃ procya tatraivāntaradhīyata|| 20.25||
gate tasmin maheṣvāse ṛṣiḥ paramapūjitaḥ|
svam āśramam upāgamya ṛṣibhyo 'akathayat tataḥ|| 20.26||
taiḥ praśastastataścaiva kālena munisattama|
yiyakṣuryajñabhūmiṃ svāṃ lāṅgalena cakarṣa tām|| 20.27||
tasyāṃ tu kṛṣyamāṇāyāṃ sītāyāṃ tat samutthitaḥ|
saṃvartakānalaprakhyaḥ kumāraḥ pratyadṛśyata|| 20.28||
sa taṃ dṛṣṭvā tathodbhūtaṃ kumāraṃ dīptatejasam|
rākṣaso 'ayam iti jñātvā bhayānnopasasāra tam|| 20.29||
kumāro 'api tathodbhūtaḥ pitaraṃ dīptatejasam|
upāsarpata dīnātmā tāta tāteti cābravīt|| 20.30||
sa tātetyucyamāno 'api yadā taṃ nābhyanandata|
tato vāyustam ākāśe śilādaṃ prāha susvaram|| 20.31||
vāyuruvāca|
śālaṅkāyana putraste yo 'asau devena śambhunā|
ayonijaḥ purā dattaḥ sa eṣa pratinandaya|| 20.32||
yasmānnandīkaraste 'ayaṃ sadaiva dvijasattama|
tasmānnandīti nāmnāyaṃ bhaviṣyati sutastava|| 20.33||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa vāyuvacanānnandinaṃ pariṣasvaje|
gṛhītvā cāśramaṃ svena so 'anayat tuṣṭivardhanam|
cūḍopanayanādīni karmāṇyasya cakāra saḥ|| 20.34||
kṛtvā cādhyāpayāmāsa vedān sāṅgānaśeṣataḥ|
āyurvedaṃ dhanurvedaṃ gāndharvaṃ śabdalakṣaṇam|| 20.35||
hastināṃ caritaṃ yacca naranāryośca lakṣaṇam|
śilpāni caiva sarvāṇi nimittajñānam eva ca|| 20.36||
bhūtagrāmacikitsāṃ ca mātR̥ṇāṃ caritaṃ ca yat|
bhujaṃgānāṃ ca sarveṣāṃ yacca kiṃcidviceṣṭitam|
abdairadhītavān sarvaṃ vyāsa pañcabhireva ca|| 20.37||
dakṣaḥ śuciradīnātmā priyavāganasūyakaḥ|
sarvalokapriyo nityaṃ manonayananandanaḥ|| 20.38||
tasyātha saptame varṣe ṛṣī divyau tapodhanau|
āśramaṃ samanuprāptau śilādasya mahaujasau|| 20.39||
tāvabhyarcya yathānyāyaṃ śilādaḥ sumahātapāḥ|
sukhāsīnau samālakṣya āsane paramārcitau|| 20.40||
mitrāvaruṇanāmānau tapoyogabalānvitau|
abhijñau sarvabhūtānāṃ trailokye sacarācare|| 20.41||
tābhyām anujñātaścaiva niṣasāda varāsane|
upaviṣṭastataḥ prīta iṣṭābhirvāgbhirastuvat|| 20.42||
tābhyāṃ pṛṣṭaśca kaccit te putrastuṣṭipradaḥ śubhaḥ|
svādhyāyaniyataḥ kaccit kacciddharmasya saṃtatiḥ|| 20.43||
kaccinna vṛddhān bālo na gurūn vāpyavamanyate|
kaccinniyamavāṃścaiva kaccit tuṣṭipradaḥ satām|| 20.44||
sa evam uktastejasvī śilādaḥ putravatsalaḥ|
uvāca guṇavān samyak kulavaṃśavivardhanaḥ|| 20.45||
tam āhūya sa tuṣṭyā tu putraṃ nandinam acyutam|
tayoḥ pādeṣu śirasā apātayata nandinam|| 20.46||
tau tu tasyāśiṣaṃ devau prayuṅkto dharmanityatām|
guruśuśrūṣaṇe bhāvaṃ lokāṃścaiva tathākṣayān|| 20.47||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śilādastām athālakṣya āśiṣaṃ devayostadā|
visṛjya nandinaṃ bhītaḥ so 'apṛcchadṛṣisattamau|| 20.48||
śilāda uvāca|
bhagavantāvṛṣī satyau gatijñau sarvadehinām|
kimarthaṃ mama putrasya dīrgham āyurubhāvapi|
prayuktavantau samyak tu nāśiṣaṃ munisattamau|| 20.49||
mitrāvaruṇaūcatuḥ|
tavaiṣa tanayastāta alpāyuḥ sarvasaṃmataḥ|
ato 'anyadvarṣam ekaṃ vai jīvitaṃ dhārayiṣyati|| 20.50||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa śokasaṃtapto nyapatadbhuvi duḥkhitaḥ|
visṛjya ṛṣiśārdūlāvekākī vilalāpa ca|| 20.51||
tasya śokādvilapataḥ svaraṃ śrutvā sutaḥ śubhaḥ|
nandī āgāt tam athāpaśyat pitaraṃ duḥkhitaṃ bhṛśam|| 20.52||
nandyuvāca|
kena tvaṃ tāta duḥkhena dūyamānaḥ prarodiṣi|
duḥkhaṃ te kuta udbhūtaṃ jñātum icchāmyahaṃ pitaḥ|| 20.53||
śilāda uvāca|
putra tvaṃ kila varṣeṇa jīvitaṃ samprahāsyasi|
ūcatustāvṛṣītyevaṃ tato māṃ kṛcchram āviśat|| 20.54||
nandyuvāca|
satyaṃ devaṛṣī tāta na tāvanṛtam ūcatuḥ|
tathāpi tu na mṛtyurme prabhaviṣyati mā śucaḥ|| 20.55||
śilāda uvāca|
kiṃ tapaḥ kiṃ parijñānaṃ ko yogaḥ kaḥ śramaśca te|
yena tvaṃ mṛtyum udyuktaṃ vañcayiṣyasi kathyatām|| 20.56||
nandyuvāca|
na tāta tapasā mṛtyuṃ vañcayiṣye na vidyayā|
mahādevaprasādena mṛtyuṃ jeṣyāmi nānyathā|| 20.57||
drakṣyāmi śaṃkaraṃ devaṃ tato mṛtyurna me bhavet|
naṣṭe mṛtyau tvayā sārdhaṃ ciraṃ vatsyāmi nirvṛtaḥ|| 20.58||
śilāda uvāca|
mayā varṣasahasreṇa tapastaptvā suduścaram|
mahādevaḥ purā dṛṣṭo labdhastvaṃ me yataḥ sutaḥ|| 20.59||
bhavāṃstu varṣeṇaikena tapasā nātibhāvitaḥ|
kathaṃ draṣṭā mahādevam etadicchāmi veditum|| 20.60||
nandyuvāca|
na tāta tapasā devo dṛśyate na ca vidyayā|
śuddhena manasā bhaktyā dṛśyate parameśvaraḥ|| 20.61||
tvayā visṛṣṭo gatvāham acireṇa trilocanam|
draṣṭā tāta na saṃdeho visṛjāśu tatastu mām|| 20.62||
tiṣṭhantaṃ māṃ yamo 'abhyetya paśyataste 'abhisaṃmatam|
na hiṃsati tathā tasmāditastāta vrajāmyaham|| 20.63||
tiṣṭhantaṃ vā śayānaṃ vā dhāvantaṃ patitaṃ tathā|
na pratīkṣati vai mṛtyuriti buddhvā śamaṃ vraja|| 20.64||
avatīrya jalaṃ divyaṃ bhāvaṃ śuddhaṃ samāsthitaḥ|
abhyasya raudram adhyāyaṃ tato drakṣyāmi śaṃkaram|| 20.65||
japataścāpi yuktasya rudrabhāvārpitasya ca|
na mṛtyukālā bahavaḥ kariṣyanti mama vyathām|| 20.66||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tam evaṃvādinaṃ matvā bruvāṇaṃ śuddhayā girā|
vyasarjayadadīnātmā kṛcchrāt putraṃ mahātapāḥ|| 20.67||
abhivandya pituḥ pādau śirasā sa mahāyaśāḥ|
pradakṣiṇaṃ samāvṛtya sampratasthe 'atiniścitaḥ|| 20.68||
abhivādya ṛṣīn sarvān sa didṛkṣurudāradhīḥ|
muniḥ sa devam agamat praṇatārtiharaṃ haram|| 20.69||
iti skandapurāṇe
viṃśatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 20.20||

ekaviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
nirgato 'atha tato nandī jagāma saritāṃ varām|
bhuvanām iti vikhyātāṃ sarvalokasukhāvahām|| 21.1||
tāṃ praviśya tato dhīmānekāgro hradam āsthitaḥ|
sa jajāpa tadā rudrān mṛtyorbhītaḥ samāhitaḥ|| 21.2||
japatā tena tatraiva tatpareṇa tadāśiṣā|
koṭirekā yadā japtā tadā devastutoṣa ha|| 21.3||
tam āgatyāha bhagavāñcharva ugraḥ kapardimān|
nandiṃstuṣṭo 'asmi bhadraṃ te varaṃ vṛṇu yathepsitam|| 21.4||
uvāca praṇato bhūtvā praṇatārtiharaṃ haram|
dvitīyāṃ japtum icchāmi koṭiṃ bhagavatāṃ vibho|
evam astviti devo 'api procyāgacchadyathāgatam|| 21.5||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
so 'avatīrya tato bhūyaḥ prayatātmā tathaiva ha|
jajāpa koṭim anyāṃ tu rudram evānucintayan|| 21.6||
dvitīyāyāṃ tataḥ koṭyāṃ sampūrṇāyāṃ vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
abhyājagāma taṃ caiva varado 'asmītyabhāṣata|| 21.7||
sa prāha bhagavan koṭiṃ tṛtīyām api kālahan|
japtum icchāmi deveśa tvatprasādādahaṃ vibho|| 21.8||
evam astviti bhūyo 'api bhagavān pratyuvāca ha|
uktvā jagāma svaṃ veśma devyā saha mahādyutiḥ|| 21.9||
tatastṛtīyāṃ rudrāṇāṃ koṭim anyāṃ jajāpa ha|
yugāntādityasaṃkāśastataḥ samabhavaddvijaḥ|| 21.10||
tasya koṭītraye vyāsa samāpte jvalanatviṣaḥ|
somaḥ saha gaṇairdevastaṃ deśam upacakrame|| 21.11||
sa taṃ kareṇa saṃgṛhya uddhṛtya salilācca ha|
saṃmṛjāno 'agrahastena nandinaṃ kālahābravīt|| 21.12||
deva uvāca|
śailāde varado 'ahaṃ te tapasānena toṣitaḥ|
sādhu japtaṃ tvayā dhīman brūhi yat te manogatam|| 21.13||
śailādiruvāca|
japeyaṃ koṭim anyāṃ tu bhūyo 'api tava tejasā|
varam etaṃ vṛṇe deva yadi tuṣṭo 'asi me vibho|| 21.14||
bhagavānuvāca|
kiṃ te japtena bhūyo 'api tuṣṭo 'asmi tava sarvathā|
yadyat tvaṃ vṛṇuṣe kāmaṃ sarvaṃ tat pradadāni te|| 21.15||
brahmatvam atha viṣṇutvam indratvam atha vāyutām|
ādityo bhava rudro vā brūhi kiṃ vā dadāni te|| 21.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto devena śirasā pādayornataḥ|
tuṣṭāva purakāmāṅgakratuparvatanāśanam|| 21.17||
nandyuvāca|
namo devātidevāya mahādevāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ kāmāṅganāśāya nīlakaṇṭhāya vai namaḥ|| 21.18||
namastuṣitanāśāya trailokyadahanāya ca|
namaḥ kālogradaṇḍāya ugradaṇḍāya vai namaḥ|| 21.19||
namo nīlaśikhaṇḍāya sahasraśirase namaḥ|
sahasrapāṇaye caiva sahasracaraṇāya ca|| 21.20||
sarvataḥpāṇipādāya sarvatokṣimukhāya ca|
sarvataḥśrutaye caiva sarvam āvṛtya tiṣṭhate|| 21.21||
namaste rukmavarṇāya tathaivātīndriyāya ca|
namaḥ kanakaliṅgāya sarvaliṅgāya vai namaḥ|| 21.22||
namaścandrārkavarṇāya yogeśāyājitāya ca|
pinākapāṇaye caiva śūlamudgarapāṇaye|| 21.23||
gadine khaḍgine caiva paraśvadhadharāya ca|
rathine varmiṇe caiva maheṣvāsāya vai namaḥ|| 21.24||
namastriśūlahastāya ugradaṇḍadharāya ca|
namo gaṇādhipataye rudrāṇāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 21.25||
namaḥ sahasranetrāya śatanetrāya vai namaḥ|
ādityānāṃ ca pataye vasūnāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 21.26||
namaḥ pṛthivyāḥ pataye ākāśapataye namaḥ|
namaḥ svarlokapataye umāyāḥ pataye namaḥ|| 21.27||
namo yogādhipataye sarvayogapradāya ca|
dhyānine dhyāyamānāya dhyānibhiḥ saṃstutāya ca|| 21.28||
mṛtyave kāladaṇḍāya yamāya ca mahātmane|
devādhipataye caiva divyasaṃhananāya ca|| 21.29||
yajñāya vasudānāya svargāyājanmadāya ca|
savitre sarvadevānāṃ dharmāyānekarūpiṇe|| 21.30||
amṛtāya vareṇyāya sarvadevastutāya ca|
brahmaṇaśca śirohartre yajñasya ca mahātmanaḥ|| 21.31||
tripuraghnāya cogrāya sarvāśubhaharāya ca|
umādehārdharūpāya lalāṭanayanāya ca|| 21.32||
mahiṣāndhakabhettāya sraṣṭre vai parameṣṭhine|
brahmaṇo gurave caiva brahmaṇo janakāya ca|| 21.33||
kumāragurave caiva kumāravaradāya ca|
haline muṣalaghnāya mahāhāsāya vai namaḥ|| 21.34||
mṛtyupāśograhastāya takṣakabrahmasūtriṇe|
savidyudghanavāhāya tathaiva vṛṣayāyine|| 21.35||
himavadvindhyavāsāya meruparvatavāsine|
kailāsavāsine caiva dhaneśvarasakhāya ca|| 21.36||
viṣṇordehārdhadattāya tasyaiva varadāya ca|
sarvabhūtāsamajñāya sarvabhūtānukampine|| 21.37||
antarbhūtādhibhūtāya prāṇināṃ jīvadāya ca|
manase manyamānāya atimānāya caiva hi|| 21.38||
budhyamānāya buddhāya draṣṭre vai cakṣuṣe namaḥ|
namaste sparśayitre ca tathaiva sparśanāya ca|| 21.39||
namaste rasayitre ca tathaiva rasanāya ca|
namo ghrāṇāya ghrātre ca śrotre śrotrāya caiva hi|
hastine caiva hastāya tathā pādāya pādine|| 21.40||
namo 'astu ānandakartre ca ānandāya ca vai namaḥ|
vāce 'atha vāgmine caiva tanmātrāya mahātmane|| 21.41||
sūkṣmāya caiva sthūlāya sattvāya rajase namaḥ|
namaśca tamase nityaṃ kṣetrajñāyājitāya ca|| 21.42||
viṣṇave lokatantrāya prajānāṃ pataye namaḥ|
manave saptaṛṣaye tapyamānāya tāpine|| 21.43||
brahmaṇyāyātha śuddhāya tathā durvāsase namaḥ|
śilpine śilpanāthāya viduṣe viśvakarmaṇe|| 21.44||
atraye bhṛgave caiva tathaivāṅgirase namaḥ|
pulahāya pulastyāya kratudakṣānalāya ca|| 21.45||
dharmāya rucaye caiva vasiṣṭhāya namo 'astu te|
bhūtāya bhūtanāthāya kuṣmāṇḍapataye namaḥ|| 21.46||
tiṣṭhate dravate caiva gāyate nṛtyate 'api ca|
avaśyāyāpyavadhyāya ajarāyāmarāya ca|| 21.47||
akṣayāyāvyayāyaiva tathāpratihatāya ca|
anāveśyāya sarveṣāṃ dṛśyāyādṛśyarūpiṇe|| 21.48||
sūkṣmebhyaścāpi sūkṣmāya sarvagāya mahātmane|
namaste bhagavaṃstryakṣa namaste bhagavañchiva|
namaste sarvalokeśa namaste lokabhāvana|| 21.49||
na me devādhipatyena brahmatvenāthavā punaḥ|
na viṣṇutvena deveśa nāpīndratvena bhūtapa|
icchāmyahaṃ taveśāna gaṇatvaṃ nityam avyayam|| 21.50||
nityaṃ tvāṃ sagaṇaṃ sāmbaṃ prasannaṃ saparicchadam|
draṣṭum icchāmi deveśa eṣa me dīyatāṃ varaḥ|| 21.51||
tvaṃ no gatiḥ purā deva tvaṃ caivārtāyanaṃ prabhuḥ|
śaraṇaṃ ca tvam evātha nānyaṃ paśyāmi karhicit|| 21.52||
tvayā tyaktasya caivāśu vināśo nātra saṃśayaḥ|
anyāṃ gatiṃ na paśyāmi yasyā ātyantikaṃ śubham|| 21.53||
anuraktaṃ ca bhaktaṃ ca tvatparaṃ tvadapāśrayam|
pratīccha māṃ sadā deva eṣa me dīyatāṃ varaḥ|| 21.54||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ prātarutthāya paṭhedavimanā naraḥ|
sa dehabhedam āsādya nandīśvarasamo bhavet|| 21.55||
yaścemaṃ śṛṇuyānnityaṃ śrāvayedvā dvijātiṣu|
so 'aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya rudraloke mahīyate|| 21.56||
śrutvā sakṛdapi hyetaṃ stavaṃ pāpapraṇāśanam|
yatra tatra mṛto vyāsa na durgatim avāpnuyāt|| 21.57||
yo 'adhītya nityaṃ stavam etam agryaṃ devaṃ sadābhyarcayate yatātmā|
kiṃ tasya yajñairvividhaiśca dānaistīrthaiḥ sutaptaiśca tathā tapobhiḥ|| 21.58||
iti skandapurāṇa ekaviṃśatimo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 21.21||

dvāviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastu devadeveśo bhaktyā paramayā yutam|
aśrupūrṇekṣaṇaṃ dīnaṃ pādayoḥ śirasā natam|| 22.1||
karābhyāṃ susukhābhyāṃ tu saṃgṛhya paramārtihā|
utthāpya nayane somaḥ aśrupūrṇe mamārja ha|| 22.2||
uvāca cainaṃ tuṣṭātmā vacasāpyāyayanniva|
nirīkṣya gaṇapān sarvān devyā saha tadā prabhuḥ|| 22.3||
deva uvāca|
jāne bhaktiṃ tava mayi jāne cārtiṃ tavānagha|
tasya sarvasya śailāde udarkaṃ saṃniśāmaya|| 22.4||
amaro jarayā tyakto nityaṃ duḥkhavivarjitaḥ|
akṣayaścāvyayaścaiva sapitā sasuhṛjjanaḥ|| 22.5||
mameṣṭo gaṇapaścaiva madvīryo matparākramaḥ|iṣṭo mama sadā caiva mama pārśvagataḥ sadā|
madrūpaścaiva bhavitā mahāyogabalānvitaḥ|| 22.6||
ṛddhimaccaiva te dvīpaṃ kṣīrodam amṛtākaram|
saṃvāsaṃ samprayacchāmi tatra raṃsyasi sarvadā|| 22.7||
kuśeśayamayīṃ mālām avamucyātmanastataḥ|
ābabandha mahātejā nandine divyarūpiṇīm|| 22.8||
sa tayā mālayā nandī babhau kaṇṭhāvasaktayā|
tryakṣo daśabhujaḥ śrīmān dvitīya iva śaṃkaraḥ|| 22.9||
tatastaṃ vai samādāya hastena bhagavān haraḥ|
uvāca brūhi kiṃ te 'adya dadāni varam uttamam|| 22.10||
āśramaścāyam atyarthaṃ tapasā tava bhāvitaḥ|
japyeśvara iti khyāto mama guhyo bhaviṣyati|| 22.11||
samantādyojanaṃ kṣetraṃ divyaṃ devagaṇairvṛtam|
siddhacāraṇasaṃkīrṇam apsarogaṇasevitam|
siddhikṣetraṃ paraṃ guhyaṃ bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|| 22.12||
karmaṇā manasā vācā yat kiṃcit kurute naraḥ|
śubhaṃ vāpyaśubhaṃ vātra sarvaṃ bhavitṛ tacchubham|| 22.13||
jāpyaṃ mānasaṃ tulyaṃ vai rudrāṇāṃ tadbhaviṣyati|
yatra tatra mṛtā martyā yāsyanti tava lokatām|| 22.14||
tato jaṭāsrutaṃ vāri gṛhītvā hāranirmalam|
uktvā nadī bhavasveti visasarja mahātapāḥ|| 22.15||
sā tato divyatoyā ca puṇyā maṇijalā śubhā|
haṃsakāraṇḍavākīrṇā cakravākopaśobhitā|
padmotpalavanopetā prāvartata mahānadī|| 22.16||
strīrūpadhāriṇī caiva prāñjaliḥ śirasā natā|
padmotpaladalābhākṣī mahādevam upasthitā|| 22.17||
tām uvāca tato devo nadīṃ svayam upasthitām|
yasmājjaṭodakāddevi pravṛttā tvaṃ śubhānane|
tasmājjaṭodā nāmnā tvaṃ bhaviṣyasi saridvarā|| 22.18||
tvayi snānaṃ tu yaḥ kuryācchuciḥ prayatamānasaḥ|
so 'aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya rudraloke mahīyate|| 22.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato devyā mahādevo nandīśvaram atiprabham|
putraste 'ayam iti procya pādayostaṃ vyanāmayat|| 22.20||
sā tam āghrāya śirasi pāṇibhyāṃ parimārjatī|
putrapremṇābhyaṣiñcat taṃ srotobhiḥ stanajaistribhiḥ|
payasā śaṅkhagaureṇa devī devaṃ nirīkṣatī|| 22.21||
tāni srotāṃsi trīṇyasyāḥ srutānyoghavatī nadī|
nadīṃ trisrotasīṃ puṇya$\uw{A\2}{2.6}$ tatastām avadaddharaḥ|| 22.22||
trisrotasaṃ nadīṃ dṛṣṭvā vṛṣaḥ paramaharṣitaḥ|
nanarda nādāt tasmācca saridanyā tato 'abhavat|| 22.23||
yasmādvṛṣabhanādena pravṛttā sā mahānadī|
tasmāḍḍhitkirikāṃ tāṃ vai uvāca vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 22.24||
jāmbūnadamayaṃ citraṃ svaṃ devaḥ paramādbhutam|
mukuṭaṃ cābabandhāsmai kuṇḍale cāmṛtodbhave|| 22.25||
taṃ tathābhyarcitaṃ vyomni dṛṣṭvā meghaḥ prabhākaraḥ|
devopavāhyaḥ siṣice sanādaḥ sataḍidguṇaḥ|| 22.26||
tasyābhiṣiktasya tadā pravṛtte srotasī bhṛśam|
yasmāt suvarṇānniḥsṛtya nadyekā sampravartata|
svarṇodaketi nāmnā tāṃ mahādevo 'abhyabhāṣata|| 22.27||
jāmbūnadamayādyasmāddvitīyā mukuṭācchubhāt|
prāvartata nadī puṇyā ūcurjambūnadīti tām|| 22.28||
etat pañcanadaṃ nāma japyeśvarasamīpagam|
vyākhyātaṃ phalam etāsāṃ jaṭodāyāṃ mahātmanā|| 22.29||
tacca pañcanadaṃ divyaṃ devaṃ japyeśvaraṃ ca tam|
trirātropoṣito gatvā snātvābhyarcya ca śūlinam|| 22.30||
brāhmaṇāṃśca tarpayitvā yatra tatra mṛto naraḥ|
nandīśvarasyānucaraḥ kṣīrodanilayo bhavet|| 22.31||
yastu japyeśvare prāṇān parityajati dustyajān|
niyamenānyathā vāpi sa me gaṇapatirbhavet|| 22.32||
nandīśvarasamo nityaḥ śāśvataḥ akṣayo 'avyayaḥ|
mama pārśvādanapagaḥ priyaḥ saṃmata eva ca|| 22.33||
japyeśvaraṃ pañcanadaṃ ca tadvai yo mānavo 'abhyetya jahāti deham|
sa me sadā syādgaṇapo variṣṭhastvayā samaḥ kāntivapuśca nityam|| 22.34||
iti skandapurāṇe dvāviṃśatimo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 22.22||

trayoviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
bhagavān devadeveśaḥ sarvabhūtapatirharaḥ|
devīm uvāca vāgīśa umāṃ girivarātmajām|| 23.1||
devi nandīśvaraṃ devam abhiṣekṣyāmi bhūtapam|
gaṇān āvāhayiṣyāmi kiṃ vā tvaṃ manyase 'avyaye|| 23.2||
devyuvāca|
saptalokādhipatyaṃ ca gaṇeśānāṃ tathaiva ca|
sarvam arhati deveśa nandī putro mamāgrajaḥ|| 23.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaḥ suraśatruniṣūdanaḥ|
prāṅmukhaḥ sa gaṇeśānām āhvānam akarot tadā|| 23.4||
tataḥ sahasraśastatra gaṇādhyakṣā mudā yutāḥ|
samprāptāḥ sarvalokeśāstacchṛṇuṣva mahāmune|| 23.5||
tataḥ karāladaśano bhṛkuṭībhūṣitānanaḥ|
śaṅkhahārāmbugauraśca daṃṣṭrī sragmī trilocanaḥ|| 23.6||
jaṭāsahasrordhvaśirā jvālākeśo mahāhanuḥ|
agnyaṅgārakanetraśca bhujagābaddhamekhalaḥ|| 23.7||
vidyujjihvo mahākāyastathā caivordhvamehanaḥ|
sarpayajñopavītī ca paraśvadhadharastathā|| 23.8||
bhujagābaddhamauñjiśca bhujagaireva kaṅkaṇaiḥ|
aṭṭahāsān sṛjānaśca aśanīpātasaṃnibhān|
diṇḍirityeva vikhyāto gaṇapaḥ samadṛśyata|| 23.9||
ātmanaḥ sadṛśānāṃ ca koṭībhirdaśabhirvṛtaḥ|
gaṇapānāṃ sureśānāṃ yogināṃ dīptatejasām|| 23.10||
tato 'aparo mahākeśo mahākāyordhvamehanaḥ|
tryakṣo 'analaśataprakhyaḥ aśanīpātanardanaḥ|| 23.11||
nṛtyan gāyaṃśca citrāṇi kurvan nāṭyānyanekaśaḥ|
jvaladaṃṣṭro mahāhāso bṛhatskandhaḥ pinākadhṛk|| 23.12||
koṭībhirdaśabhiḥ sārdhaṃ dviguṇābhirmahātmanām|
gaṇānāṃ citrarūpāṇāṃ yugapat sampradṛśyata|| 23.13||
siṃhāsyagajakokāsyairdvīpiśārdūlakānanaiḥ|
so 'aṣāḍhirnāma gaṇapo vyāsa tatra samāgataḥ|| 23.14||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
athānyo vyāsa samprāpto yugāntādityasaprabhaḥ|
śatayojanabāhuśca digvāsāścordhvamehanaḥ|| 23.15||
atidīrgho 'atimeḍhraśca lambabhrūḥ sthūlanāsikaḥ|
vṛttāsyaśca mahākṣaśca bhṛkuṭīsaṃhatānanaḥ|| 23.16||
pañcayojanavistīrṇo dīrgho vai tāvadeva ca|
daṃṣṭrāścatasro vaktreṇa bibhracchaṅkhendupāṇḍarāḥ|| 23.17||
pañcajihvordhvakarṇaśca pāśahasto manojavaḥ|
vṛtaḥ koṭīśatenaiva sadṛśānām adṛśyata|| 23.18||
bhārabhūtīti vikhyāto mahāyogabalānvitaḥ|
gaṇapo devadevasya samīpaṃ so 'abhyagacchata|| 23.19||
tataḥ kundenduśaṅkhābhaṃ himarāśyambusaṃnibham|
mṛṇālasphaṭikābhaṃ ca bhasmakakṣāvalambanam|| 23.20||
gṛhītvā cāśanīhāsaṃ tripādaṃ cīravāsasam|
śatodaraṃ triśirasaṃ trinetraṃ cordhvamūrdhajam|| 23.21||
jvālāmālāgrakeśaṃ ca vyāghracarmājināmbaram|
vāyuvegaṃ mahāhāsaṃ bhujagābaddhamekhalam|| 23.22||
mahoragakṛtāpīḍaṃ śaṅkukarṇordhvamehanam|
bhasmapraharaṇaṃ caiva mahādaṃṣṭraṃ mahāhanum|| 23.23||
mahāgaṇapatiṃ vīraṃ jvara ityeva viśrutam|
koṭīśatavṛtaṃ taṃ ca gaṇapaṃ so 'anvapaśyata|| 23.24||
tato 'aparaḥ saumyarūpo bhasmadigdhāṅga eva ca|
triśūlapāṇirdigvāsā mahāyogabalānvitaḥ|| 23.25||
bahuveṣadharaścaiva dhyānayogaparāyaṇaḥ|
somavarṇa iti khyātaḥ koṭīśatavṛtaḥ prabhuḥ|
tādṛśānāṃ gaṇādhyakṣo devenāhūta āgataḥ|| 23.26||
athāparo mahākāyaḥ śūlapāṇirmahābalaḥ|
yugāntānalasaṃkāśaḥ sthiraḥ sthirayaśobalaḥ|| 23.27||
candramaulirmahākeśaścaturbāhurvilohitaḥ|
ekapādairmahākāyaistryakṣaistaiḥ śūlapāṇibhiḥ|| 23.28||
vṛtaḥ koṭīśatenaiva sthāṇustatrābhyavartata|
samahāpārṣado rudraḥ sarvāsuranibarhaṇaḥ|| 23.29||
tato 'aparaḥ paṭṭisena hrasvapādodaraḥ śuciḥ|
sahasrabāhucaraṇaḥ sahasrākṣaḥ pratāpavān|| 23.30||
karāladaśanaścaiva kṛṣṇasarpāmbaracchadaḥ|
tryakṣaścandrakṛtāpīḍaḥ kaṇṭhamālāvibhūṣitaḥ|| 23.31||
ugrasena iti khyātaḥ koṭīśatavṛtaḥ sa ca|
āgāt samīpaṃ devasya āhūtaḥ svayam īśvaraḥ|| 23.32||
tato 'aparaḥ samāpede devaṃ candrārdhadhāriṇam|
caturvaktro mahātejāścaturviṃśekṣaṇaḥ prabhuḥ|| 23.33||
sahasrabāhurjvālāsyo mahānetrordhvamehanaḥ|
karāladaśanaścaiva śaṅkukarṇo mahānakhaḥ|| 23.34||
asipāṇirmahātejāḥ śatapādaḥ śatodaraḥ|
vidyutkeśo 'atihāsaśca tathaivobhayatogatiḥ|| 23.35||
ajaikapāditi khyāto vṛtaḥ koṭīśatena saḥ|
kāñcanopalavṛkṣāḍhyaḥ samegha iva parvataḥ|| 23.36||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
āgāt tato 'aparo vyāsa gaṇapaḥ sumahābalaḥ|
sarvatovadanaḥ śrīmān sarvataḥpāṇipādadhṛk|| 23.37||
hrasvabāhūrupādaśca aśaniṃ dhārayañchubham|
śatairvṛtaśca koṭīnām aṣṭābhistu ātmanaḥ samaiḥ|
nikumbha iti vikhyātaḥ śatapādodarānanaḥ|| 23.38||
āgāt tato 'aparaścāpi vidyutkeśo mahābalaḥ|
candramālādharo ghoraḥ prahasan pravicālayan|| 23.39||
daṇḍadhārī mahāvaktraḥ śaṅkhakundendusaprabhaḥ|
gaṇakoṭīśatavṛtaḥ paramaṃ paratāpanaḥ|| 23.40||
tato 'aparaḥ sahasreṇa koṭīnāṃ gaṇapo vṛtaḥ|
sūryamālāsrajaṃ bibhradājagāma mahātapāḥ|| 23.41||
sa sūryāpyāyano nāma devasya paramapriyaḥ|
dhanuṣpāṇirmahātejā viśrutaḥ samahādyutiḥ|| 23.42||
tathānyaḥ sarpamālaśca cakrābharaṇa eva ca|
cakrāyudho mahātejā hrasvapādakaṭīkaraḥ|| 23.43||
sa nāmnā viśruto loke grahāpyāyana ityuta|
gaṇakoṭiśataiḥ ṣaḍbhirvṛtaḥ samanudhāvata|| 23.44||
śaṅkukarṇo 'abhyayāccaiva gaṇakoṭyā mahābalaḥ|
nandikaścāpi daśabhiḥ piṅgākṣo 'aṣṭābhireva ca|
vināyakaścatuḥṣaṣṭyā kuṣmāṇḍo nāma viśrutaḥ|| 23.45||
hiraṇyavarṇaḥ ṣaḍbhiśca ekapādastathaiva ca|
dhūmrakeśo dvādaśabhiḥ patākī daśabhistathā|| 23.46||
sahasraghaṇṭo 'aṣṭādaśabhistapaḥ pañcabhireva ca|
sahasraśīrṣaḥ ṣaḍbhiśca bhavaḥ koṭiśatāvṛtaḥ|| 23.47||
varo daśabhirabhyāgāt kumbhakarṇastathāṣṭabhiḥ|
viṣvaksenaḥ sahasreṇa annadastu śatena vai|| 23.48||
āveśanī tathāṣṭābhiḥ saptabhiśca pravartanaḥ|
mahāravaḥ sahasreṇa koṭīnāṃ gaṇapo vṛtaḥ|| 23.49||
caturmukho dvādaśabhistathā bāhūpahārakaḥ|
mahākālaḥ śatenaiva tathāgniśikharo gaṇaḥ|| 23.50||
ādityamūrdhā koṭyā ca tathā caiva dhanāvahaḥ|
saṃnāmaśca śatenaiva kukkuṭo 'aṣṭābhireva ca|| 23.51||
kundaśca pañcadaśabhistathā saṃkoṭako 'aparaḥ|
amoghabhūtiḥ koṭyā ca tathā dvau meghabhūtikau|| 23.52||
ekapādo 'aparaḥ ṣaṣṭyā tathā sapta$\uw{$śirā gaṇa }${3.2}$ḥ|
mahābalaśca navabhirapasmāraśca viśrutaḥ|| 23.53||
nīlo navatyā deveśaḥ pūrṇabhadrastathaiva ca|
nirṛtiścaiva saptatyā koṭīnām abhyagāt saha|| 23.54||
koṭīkoṭīsahasrāṇāṃ śatairviṃśatibhirvṛtāḥ|
ītayastatra cājagmurmahāyogabalānvitāḥ|| 23.55||
bhūtāḥ koṭisahasreṇa pramathāḥ koṭibhistribhiḥ|
vīrabhadraścatuḥṣaṣṭyā vṛṣabhaśca mahābalaḥ|| 23.56||
meghaḥ saudāmanīmālo navatyā saṃvṛto 'abhyagāt|
prabhākaraśca viṃśatyā viṭpatiśca mahābalaḥ|| 23.57||
giriko meghanādaśca udaro maṇireva ca|
kāṣṭhakarṇaśca divyātmā bilvarūpaśca viśrutaḥ|| 23.58||
śatamanyustathā caiva pañcākṣaścaiva vīryavān|
tālaketuśca ṣaṇḍaśca kāpālī gajanāśanaḥ|| 23.59||
saṃvartakastathā caitrastrailokyadahanastathā|
lokāntakaśca dīptātmā hemakuṇḍala eva ca|| 23.60||
mṛtyuścaiva yamaścaiva kālo viṣaharastathā|
śatamāyo mahāmāyaḥ sarvatrāśaraṇastathā|
ekaśṛṅgī ca vikhyātastathā bhṛṅgiriṭiśca yaḥ|| 23.61||
ete cānye ca gaṇapā guhyā ye ca mahābalāḥ|
tatrājagmurmudā yuktāḥ sarve citrāstrayodhinaḥ|| 23.62||
gāyantaśca dravantaśca nṛtyantaśca mahābalāḥ|
mukhāḍambaravādyāni nādayantastathaiva ca|| 23.63||
rathairnāgairhayaiścaiva vāyumarkaṭavāhanāḥ|
vyāghrasiṃhabiḍālaiśca sarpaiḥ pakṣibhireva ca|| 23.64||
bherīśaṅkhamṛdaṅgaiśca paṇavānakagomukhaiḥ|
vāditrairvividhaiścaiva paṭahairekapuṣkaraiḥ|| 23.66||
bherījharjharasaṃnādairāḍambarakaḍiṇḍimaiḥ|
maḍḍukairveṇuvīṇābhirvivṛṣaistuṇavairapi|| 23.67||
darduraistālaghātaiśca kacchapaiḥ paṇavairapi|
vādyamānairmahāyogā ājagmurdevasaṃsadam|| 23.68||
te viśvakarmāṇam amitrasāhā viśveśam ekākṣaram avyayaṃ ca|
sahasranetrapratimātibhāsvarāḥ praṇemuruccairapi cābhineduḥ|| 23.69||
iti skandapurāṇe
trayoviṃśatimo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 23.23||
puṣpakena vimānena tathā mattadvipena ca|| 23.70||
channaṃ kṛtvā tathākāśaṃ kiṃnaroragacāraṇāḥ|
nānāvimānam ārūḍhāḥ koṭiśastatra cāpare|}

caturviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te gaṇeśā mahāsattvāḥ sarve deveśvareśvarāḥ|
praṇamya devaṃ devīṃ ca idaṃ vacanam abruvan|| 24.1||
bhagavan devatārighna devadevāmbikāpate|
kim arthaṃ vayam āhūtā ājñāpaya kṛtaṃ hi tat|| 24.2||
kiṃ sāgarāñchoṣayāmo yamaṃ vā saha kiṃkaraiḥ|
hanmo mṛtyum utāmṛtyurna bhavatvadya padmajaḥ|| 24.3||
baddhvendraṃ saha devaiśca saviṣṇuṃ saha vāyunā|
ānayāmaḥ susaṃkruddhā daityān vā saha dānavaiḥ|| 24.4||
kasyādya vyasanaṃ ghoraṃ kariṣyāmastavājñayā|
kasya vādyotsavaṃ deva sarvakāmasamṛddhimat|| 24.5||
tāṃstathāvādinaḥ sarvān namato bhaktavatsalaḥ|
uvāca devaḥ sampūjya gaṇān gaṇapatirbhavaḥ|| 24.6||
deva uvāca|
śṛṇudhvaṃ yatkṛte yūyam ihāhūtā jagaddhitāḥ|
śrutvā ca prayatātmānaḥ kurudhvaṃ tadaśaṅkitāḥ|| 24.7||
nandīśvaro 'ayaṃ putro naḥ sarveṣām īśvareśvaraḥ|
priyo 'agranāyakaścaiva senānīrvaḥ samāhitaḥ|| 24.8||
tam imaṃ mama saṃdeśādyūyaṃ sarve 'abhisaṃmatāḥ|
senānyam abhiṣiñcadhvaṃ mahāyogapatiṃ patim|| 24.9||
adyaprabhṛti yuṣmākam ayaṃ nandīśvaraḥ śubhaḥ|
priyo gauravayuktaśca senānīramaraḥ prabhuḥ|| 24.10||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam ukte bhagavatā gaṇapāḥ sarva eva te|
evam astviti saṃmantrya sambhārān āharaṃstataḥ|| 24.11||
tasya rūpāśrayaṃ divyaṃ jāmbūnadamayaṃ śubham|
āsanaṃ merusaṃkāśaṃ manoramam athāharan|| 24.12||
śātakumbhamayaṃ cāpi cārucāmīkaraprabham|
muktādāmāvalambaṃ ca maṇiratnāvabhāsitam|| 24.13||
stambhaiśca vaiḍūryamayaiḥ kiṅkiṇījālasaṃvṛtam|
cāruratnakasaṃyuktaṃ maṇḍapaṃ viśvatomukham|
kṛtvā cakruśca tanmadhye tadāsanavaraṃ śubham|| 24.14||
tasyāgrataḥ pādapīṭhaṃ nīlaṃ vajrāvabhāsitam|
cakruḥ pādapratiṣṭhārthaṃ kalaśau cāsya pārśvagau|
sampūrṇau paramāmbhobhiraravindāvṛtānanau|| 24.15||
agrato 'agniṃ samādhāya vṛṣabhaṃ cāpi pārśvataḥ|
savatsāṃ surabhiṃ cāpi tasya pārśve 'atha dakṣiṇe|| 24.16||
chattraṃ śataśalākaṃ ca jāmbūnadamayaṃ śubham|
śaṅkhahārāmbugaureṇa pṛṣṭhenābhivirājitam|| 24.17||
vyajanaṃ candraśubhraṃ ca hemadaṇḍaṃ sucārumat|
mālāṃ kuśeśayānāṃ ca bhramarāvalisevitām|| 24.18||
āninyustatra gaṇapā nandyāvartāṃśca kāñcanān|
punarvasuṃ ca puṣyaṃ ca dvau matsyau varuṇālayau|| 24.19||
svastikaṃ vardhamānaṃ ca śrīvatsaṃ caiva kāñcanam|
kīcakā veṇavaścaiva kanyā caivābhipūjitā|| 24.20||
airāvataṃ supratīkaṃ gajāvetau ca pūjitau|
dhvajaṃ ca pūjitaṃ divyaṃ śaṅkhaṃ caivenduvarcasam|| 24.21||
kalaśānāṃ sahasraṃ ca kāñcanānāṃ suvarcasām|
rājatānāṃ sahasraṃ ca pārthivānāṃ tathaiva ca|| 24.22||
tāmrāṇām atha divyānāṃ sahasram analatviṣām|
vāsoyugaṃ vṛkṣajaṃ ca virajaḥ sūkṣmam eva ca|| 24.23||
mukuṭaṃ kāñcanaṃ caiva sukṛtaṃ viśvakarmaṇā|
kuṇḍale cāmale divye vajraṃ caiva varāyudham|| 24.24||
paṭṭisaṃ ca mahaddivyaṃ śūlaṃ cāśanim eva ca|
jāmbūnadamayaṃ sūtraṃ keyūradvayam eva ca|| 24.25||
hāraṃ ca maṇicitrāṅgaṃ rocanārucakaṃ tathā|
darbhāṃśca divyāṃ samidham ājyaṃ dhūpam athāpi ca|
samantānninyuravyagrā gaṇapā devasaṃmatāḥ|| 24.27||
tato diśaḥ samudrāśca varuṇaḥ sadhaneśvaraḥ|
yamo 'agnirvasavaścaiva candrādityau grahaiḥ saha|| 24.28||
tārārūpāṇi sarvāṇi nakṣatrāṇi dhruvastathā|
rudrā rakṣāṃsi yakṣāśca aśvinau daityadānavāḥ|| 24.29||
gandharvāpsarasaścaiva nāradaḥ parvatastathā|
pṛthivī ca samudrāśca varṣāṇi girayastathā|| 24.30||
vṛkṣāśca vīrudhaścaiva oṣadhyaśca mahābalāḥ|
nadyaḥ sarvāḥ samājagmuḥ paśavaścaiva sarvaśaḥ|| 24.31||
lokasya mātaraścaiva pṛthivī svarga eva ca|
bhūtāni prakṛtiścaiva indriyāṇi ca sarvaśaḥ|| 24.32||
tīrthāni caiva sarvāṇi dānāni vividhāni ca|
ṛco yajūṃṣi sāmāni atharvāṅgirasāv api|| 24.33||
yajñāśca kratavaścaiva iṣṭayo niyamāstathā|
chandāṃsi caiva sarvāṇi piśācā devayonayaḥ|
brahmā ca ṛṣayaścaiva viṣṇuḥ sānucarastathā|| 24.34||
teṣu āgateṣu sarveṣu bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|
sarvakāryavidhiṃ kartum ādideśa pitāmaham|| 24.35||
ekaikaṃ kalaśaṃ tatra sarvauṣadhisamanvitam|
kṛtvādbhiḥ pūrayitvā ca kuśeśayamukhāvṛtam|| 24.36||
jayāṃ ca vijayāṃ caiva siṃhīṃ vyāghrīṃ tathaiva ca|
suvarcalāṃ śaṅkhapuṣpīṃ viṣṇukrāntāṃ punarnavām|| 24.37||
kumārīṃ candrakāntāṃ ca mṛtasaṃjīvanīm api|
ādityavarcasaṃ caiva amṛtāṃ śrīniketanām|| 24.38||
tathā kumudvatīṃ caiva prākṣipaṃsteṣvathauṣadhīḥ|
pārthiveṣu tadā vyāsa sarveṣveva gaṇeśvarāḥ|| 24.39||
sauvarṇeṣu tu sarveṣu tīrthāni vividhāni ca|
dānāni caiva sarvāṇi bhagavān saṃnyaveśayat|| 24.40||
rājateṣu ca kumbheṣu mantrāṃśchandāṃsi caiva ha|
kratūnanyāṃśca vividhā iṣṭīḥ kāmyāṃstathetarān|| 24.41||
audumbareṣu sarveṣu saritaḥ sāgarāṃstathā|
tapāṃsi niyamāṃścaiva bhagavānabhyavinyasat|| 24.42||
ekaikaṃ kalaśaṃ tatra abhipūryābhimantrya ca|
veṣṭayitvā ca sūtreṇa devebhyaḥ pradadau vibhuḥ|| 24.43||
sa jagrāha tadā brahmā ekaṃ kalaśam ātmanā|
viṣṇave ca dadāvekam ekam indrāya dhīmate|
gaṇapebhyastathā cānyānṛṣibhyaśca pitāmahaḥ|| 24.44||
tatastam āsane tasminnupaveśya mahāmanāḥ|
arcayitvā tato brahmā svayam evābhyaṣiñcata|| 24.45||
tato viṣṇustataḥ śakro ṛṣayaśca sahāmaraiḥ|
gaṇādhipāśca sarve te abhyaṣiñcanta nandinam|| 24.46||
vāsoyugaṃ ca taddivyaṃ gandhān divyāṃstathaiva ca|
keyūre kuṇḍale caiva mukuṭaṃ hāram eva ca|
paṭṭisaṃ śūlavajre ca aśanīṃ ca dadau svayam|| 24.47||
chattraṃ jagrāha devendro vāyurvyajanam eva ca|
ṛṣayastuṣṭuvuścaiva pitāmahapurogamāḥ|| 24.48||
viṣṇuruvāca|
namaḥ kuṣmāṇḍarājāya vajrodyatakarāya ca|
śālaṅkāyanapautrāya halamārgotthitāya ca|| 24.49||
śilādasya ca putrāya rudrajapyakarāya ca|
rudrabhaktāya devāya namo 'antarjalaśāyine|| 24.50||
gaṇānāṃ pataye caiva bhūtānāṃ pataye namaḥ|
umāputrāya devāya paṭṭisāyudhadhāriṇe|| 24.51||
namo daṃṣṭrākarālāya lalāṭanayanāya ca|
pramathāya vareṇyāya īśānāyārpitāya ca|| 24.52||
dvārādhyakṣāya śūrāya suyaśāpataye namaḥ|
namaḥ pravaramālāya kṣīrodanilayāya ca|| 24.53||
mahāgaṇādhipataye mahāyogeśvarāya ca|
diṇḍimuṇḍāya caṇḍāya ekākṣararatāya ca|| 24.54||
akṣayāyāmṛtāyaiva ajarāyāmarāya ca|
paśūnāṃ pataye caiva jetre mṛtyostathaiva ca|| 24.55||
namaḥ pavanavegāya sarvajñāyājitāya ca|
anekaśirase caiva anekacaraṇāya ca|| 24.56||
kirīṭine kuṇḍaline mahāparighabāhave|
sarvān devān gaṇāṃścaiva pāhi deva namo 'astu te|| 24.57||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ stutvā tato devastasmai vyāsa mahātmane|
prāñjaliḥ prayato bhūtvā jayaśabdaṃ cakāra ha|| 24.58||
tato gaṇā jayeti ūcustato devāstato 'asurāḥ|
tataḥ sarvāṇi bhūtāni brahmā śakrastathaiva ca|| 24.59||
tataḥ śaṅkhāṃśca bherīṃśca paṭahāḍambarāṃstathā|
vaṃśāṃśca paṇavāṃścaiva kṛkavān goviṣāṇikān|| 24.60||
diṇḍimān veṇukāṃścaiva mardalāṃścaiva sarvaśaḥ|
avādayanta gaṇapā harṣayanto mudā yutāḥ|| 24.61||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
nandīśvarasya ya imaṃ stavaṃ devābhinirmitam|
paṭheta satataṃ martyaḥ sa gacchenmama lokatām|| 24.62||
namo nandīśvarāyeti kṛtvā yaḥ svapnam ācaret|
tasya kuṣmāṇḍarājebhyo na bhayaṃ vidyate kvacit|| 24.63||
yatrāyaṃ sthāpyate nityaṃ stavaḥ paramapūjitaḥ|
na bhayaṃ tatra bhavati grahebhyo vyāsa sarvadā|| 24.64||
nandīśvaraṃ ye praṇamanti martyā nityaṃ prasannendriyaśuddhasattvāḥ|
te devadevasya sahādriputryā iṣṭā variṣṭhāśca gaṇā bhavanti|| 24.65||
iti skandapurāṇe caturviṃśatimo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 24.24||

pañcaviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastatrāgatān devān devatādhipatirbhavaḥ|
marutaḥ prāha sampūjya kanyārthaṃ sadasatpatiḥ|| 25.1||
maruto ye mahāvegā mahāsattvā mahaujasaḥ|
āmantrya nāmnā tān īśaḥ saśakraḥ sapitāmahaḥ|| 25.2||
yuṣmākaṃ suyaśā kanyā subhagā divyarūpiṇī|
dātum arhatha tāṃ subhrūṃ snuṣāṃ mahyaṃ mahābalāḥ|| 25.3||
maruta ūcuḥ|
tvam asmākaṃ ca tasyāśca sarvasya jagatastathā|
prabhaviṣṇustrilokeśa na tu yācitum arhasi|| 25.4||
tvayaiva deyā grāhyā ca tvaṃ no gatiranuttamā|
mā naḥ parāniveśāna yācanena vibhāvaya|| 25.5||
pitā naḥ kaśyapaḥ śrīmān marīciśca pitāmahaḥ|
pitāmahapitā brahmā tasyāpi tvaṃ pitāmahaḥ|
sa tvaṃ pitāmaho 'asmākaṃ na parān kartum arhasi|| 25.6||
sa evam ukto deveśo marudbhirdevasattamaiḥ|
suyaśāṃ marutāṃ kanyām ānayāmāsa tatkṣaṇāt|| 25.7||
svayaṃ hotāsya tatrāsīdbrahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
kaśyapaśca tathodgātā atriḥ sāma svayaṃ jagau|
atharvāṅgirasau devau brahmatvam api cakratuḥ|| 25.8||
nāradaḥ parvataścaiva citrasenaśca gāyanaḥ|
viśvāvasuu ruciścaiva hāhā hūhū tathaiva ca|| 25.9||
tathā śāliśirā yaśca viśruto gaṇḍamaṇḍakaḥ|
ītiścaivendravāhaśca yajñavāho 'atha dakṣiṇaḥ|
ete cānye ca gandharvā jagurmadhurakaṇṭhinaḥ|| 25.10||
urvaśī caiva rambhā ca ghṛtācī pūrvacittyapi|
tilottamā ca viśvācī anyāścāpsarasaḥ śubhāḥ|
anṛtyanta mahābhāgā nṛttaṃ suramanoharam|| 25.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam abhavadvyāsa vivāhastasya dhīmataḥ|
nandino gaṇamukhyasya anaupamyo hyaninditaḥ|| 25.12||
tataḥ sa tu kṛtodvāho nandī gatvā mahāmanāḥ|
pādān vavande devasya devyā brahmaṇa eva ca|
śilādasya ca lokeśaḥ śriyā paramayā yutaḥ|| 25.13||
deva uvāca|
varaṃ vṛṇīṣva putra tvaṃ snuṣā ceyaṃ tava priyā|
varaṃ dadāmi te vatsa anayā saha m īpsitam|| 25.14||
nandyuvāca|
bhagavan yadi tuṣṭo 'asi tvayi bhaktirdṛḍhāstu me|
sadā ca tuṣṭo bhava me sāmbaḥ saha gaṇeśvaraiḥ|| 25.15||
pitaraṃ caiva me deva utpādakam imaṃ prabho|
anugraheṇa yuktena yoktum arhasi kāmada|| 25.16||
deva uvāca|
sadāhaṃ tava nandīśa sutuṣṭaḥ sagaṇeśvaraḥ|
pārvatyā sahito dhīmannidaṃ ca śṛṇu me vacaḥ|| 25.17||
sadeṣṭaśca variṣṭhaśca paramaiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|
mahāyogī maheṣvāso mahābalaparākramaḥ|| 25.18||
ajayyaścaiva jetā ca pūjyejyaśca sadā bhava|
ahaṃ yatra bhavāṃstatra yatra tvaṃ tatra cāpyaham|| 25.19||
parvataṃ cāsya vaibhrājaṃ kāmagaṃ sarvakāñcanam|
upetaṃ bhavanairdivyaiḥ prayacchāmi janāvṛtam|
tenāyaṃ sarvalokeṣu cariṣyati yathepsitam|| 25.21||
sthānaṃ śrīparvate cāsya bhaviṣyati supūjitam|
bhṛgau tasmiṃśca yaḥ prāṇāṃstyakṣyate vai sudhārmikaḥ|
sa kāmacārī vaibhrāje gaṇapo 'asya bhaviṣyati|| 25.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato devī mahābhāgā śailāderadadadvaram|
so 'abravīt tvayi bhaktirme sadaivānapagā bhavet|| 25.23||
tato marutsutā caiva ubhābhyām api coditā|
varaṃ vṛṇu yatheṣṭaṃ vai tāvidaṃ pratyuvāca ha|| 25.24||
yuvayorastu bhaktirme tathā bhartari caiva hi|
nityaṃ cānapagā syānme dharme ca matiruttamā|
etadicchāmi deveśau varaṃ varasahasradau|| 25.25||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastāvevam etat te bhaviteti śucismite|
ūcaturmuditau devau snuṣāṃ tāṃ varavarṇinīm|| 25.26||
gaṇāścāsya tato 'abhyetya sarve devapriyepsayā|
varaṃ dadurmahāsattvāḥ sa vavre kāñcanaprabhaḥ|| 25.27||
yuṣmāsu mama bhaktiśca aiśvaryaṃ cāpi saṃmatam|
vaśyāśca yūyaṃ sarve me priyo yuṣmākam eva ca|| 25.28||
gaṇā ūcuḥ|
bhavān mantānumantā ca gatirāgatireva ca|
asmākam īśaḥ sarveṣāṃ devānām api ceśvaraḥ|| 25.29||
kuṣmāṇḍānāṃ variṣṭhaśca rudrāṇāṃ tvaṃ mahābalaḥ|
ītīnāṃ dvārapālaśca pramathānāṃ tathaiva ca|| 25.30||
mahābalo mahāyogī senānīstvaṃ hi no mataḥ|
tvaṃ bhūto bhūtanetā ca nāyako 'atha vināyakaḥ|| 25.31||
grahāṇām adhipaścaiva ugradaṇḍadharastathā|
tvam agrayodhī śatrughnastvaṃ vīrastvaṃ divaspatiḥ|| 25.32||
mahānubhāvastvaṃ caiva kṣīrodanilayaśca ha|
japyeśvaraniketaśca japyeśvaravibhāvitaḥ|| 25.33||
bhāvanaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ varado varadārcitaḥ|
asmākaṃ varadaścaiva bhava bhūteśvara prabho|| 25.34||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evaṃ gaṇapaiḥ sarvaiḥ stuto nandīśvaro vibhuḥ|
uvāca praṇataḥ sarvān brūta kiṃ karavāṇi vaḥ|| 25.35||
ta evamuktā gaṇapāḥ sarva eva mahābalāḥ|
ūcustaṃ divyabhāvajñā devadevasya saṃnidhau|| 25.36||
tvam asmākaṃ gaṇādhyakṣaḥ kṛto devena śambhunā|
asmābhiścābhiṣiktastvaṃ nāyako dharmadāyakaḥ|| 25.37||
sa tvaṃ śivaśca saumyaśca guṇavānaguṇeṣvapi|
kṣamāśaucadamopeto bhava naḥ priyakṛt sadā|| 25.38||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evamuktastadā sarvān praṇamya bahumānataḥ|
śirasyañjalim ādhāya gaṇapānastuvat tadā|| 25.39||
nandyuvāca|
namo vaḥ sarvabhūtebhyo namo yogibhya eva ca|
namaścāpyaniketebhyo yogīśebhyo namastathā|| 25.40||
namaḥ kāmacarebhyaśca nama ugrebhya eva ca|
mṛtyubhyaśca yamebhyaśca kālebhyaśca namo namaḥ|| 25.41||
namaḥ kāñcanamālebhyaḥ sarvadharmibhya eva ca|
namo vo vadhakebhyaśca avadhyebhyastathaiva ca|| 25.42||
namo valkalavāsebhyaḥ kṛttivāsebhya eva ca|
namaḥ śvetāmbarasragbhyaścitrasragbhyo namo namaḥ|| 25.44||
dhāvadbhyaśca dravadbhyaśca prasthitebhyo namo namaḥ|
namo munibhyo gāyadbhyo japadbhyaśca namo namaḥ|| 25.45||
namo mārjārarūpebhyaḥ kākakokebhya eva ca|
namo daivatarūpebhyaḥ pavanebhyastathaiva ca|| 25.47||
namo 'agnibhyastathādbhyaśca varuṇebhyastathaiva ca|
namo dhaneśarūpebhyaḥ sarvarūpibhya eva ca|| 25.48||
namaścodaravaktrebhyaḥ sarvavaktrebhya eva ca|
namo vāmanarūpebhyo vāmarūpebhya eva ca|| 25.49||
devāsuramanuṣyāṇām āpyāyibhyo namo namaḥ|
namo vaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ namo vaḥ sarvataḥ śubhāḥ|| 25.50||
grahebhyaśca namo vo 'astu mokṣebhyaśca namastathā|
śubhebhyaśca namo vo 'astu aśubhebhyastathaiva ca|
mama saumyāḥ śivāścaiva bhavantu gaṇanāyakāḥ|| 25.51||
iti stutā gaṇapatayo mahābalāḥ śubhairvacobhiḥ suraśatrunāśanāḥ|
diśantu me sukham atulaṃ sukhapradā balaṃ ca vīryaṃ sthiratāṃ ca saṃyuge|| 25.52||
tapo 'akṣayaṃ sthānam athātulāṃ gatiṃ yaśastathāgryaṃ bahu dharmanityatām|
diśantu sarvaṃ manasepsitaṃ ca me sureśvarāḥ puṣṭim anuttamāṃ tathā|| 25.53||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
imau nandigaṇendrāṇāṃ stavau yo 'adhyeti nityaśaḥ|
so 'aśvamedhāvabhṛthavat sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 25.54||
sandhyāyām aparasyāṃ tu japan pāpaṃ divākṛtam|
pūrvasyāṃ saṃtyajedvāpi sarvarātrikṛtaṃ japan|| 25.55||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste gaṇapāḥ sarve saṃstutāstena dhīmatā|
nisṛṣṭāśca tadā jagmuḥ praṇipatya vṛṣadhvajam|| 25.56||
devāśca sarvalokāśca tato devaḥ svayaṃ prabhuḥ|
sṛṣṭvā nandīśvaragṛhaṃ pradāya ca mahāmanāḥ|
īpsitaṃ saha devyā vai jagāma sthānam avyayam|| 25.57||
ya imaṃ nandino janma varadānaṃ tathaiva ca|
abhiṣekaṃ vivāhaṃ ca paṭhedvā śrāvayīta vā|
brāhmaṇaḥ sa mṛto yāti nandīśvarasalokatām|| 25.58||
yo niyatastu paṭhet prayatātmā sarvam imaṃ praṇato bhavabhaktyā|
so 'api gataḥ paralokavicārī nandisamo 'anucaro hi mama syāt|| 25.59||
iti skandapurāṇe
pañcaviṃśatimo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 25.25||

ṣaḍ{}viṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ nandīśvaro vyāsa utpanno 'anucaraśca ha|
abhavaddevadevasya senāpatye 'abhiṣecitaḥ|| 26.1||
vyāsa uvāca|
devyā sahātha bhagavān āsīnastatra kāmadaḥ|
akarot kiṃ mahādeva etadicchāmi veditum|| 26.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
bhagavān himavacchṛṅge śarvo devyāḥ priyepsayā|
gaṇeśairvividhākārairhāsaṃ saṃjanayanmuhuḥ|| 26.3||
devīṃ bālendutilako rāmayacca rarāma ca|
mahānubhāvaiḥ sarvajñaiḥ kāmarūpadharaiḥ śubhaiḥ|| 26.4||
atha devī āsasādaikā mātaraṃ parameśvarī|
āsīnāṃ kāñcane śubhre āsane paramārcite|| 26.5||
atha dṛṣṭvā satīṃ devīm āgatāṃ tu surūpiṇīm|
āsanena mahārheṇa sampādayadaninditām|| 26.6||
āsīnāṃ tāṃ ca sovāca menā himavataḥ priyā|
cirasyāgamanaṃ hyadya tava putri śubhekṣaṇe|
daridrakrīḍanaistvaṃ hi bhartrā krīḍasi saṃgatā|| 26.7||
ye daridrā bhavanti sma tathaiva ca nirāśrayāḥ|
ume ta evaṃ krīḍanti yathā tava patiḥ śubhe|| 26.8||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
saivam uktā tu mātrātha nātihṛṣṭamanābhavat|
mahatyākṣamayā yuktā na kiṃcit tām uvāca ha|| 26.9||
visṛṣṭā sā tadā mātrā gatvā devam uvāca ha|
bhagavan devadeveśa neha vatsyāmi bhūdhare|
anyaṃ vṛṇu mamāvāsaṃ bhuvaneśa mahādyute|| 26.10||
deva uvāca|
sadā tvam ucyamānā vai mayā vāsārtham īśvari|
anyatra rocitavatī nāvāsaṃ devi karhicit|| 26.11||
idānīṃ svayam eva tvaṃ vāsam anyatra śobhane|
kasmānmṛgayase devi brūhi tanme śucismite|| 26.12||
devyuvāca|
gṛhaṃ gatāhaṃ deveśa pituradya mahātmanaḥ|
dṛṣṭā ca me tatra mātā vijane lokabhāvanī|| 26.13||
āsanādibhirabhyarcya sā mām evam abhāṣata|
ume tava sadā bhartā daridrakrīḍanaiḥ śubhe|
krīḍate na hi devānāṃ krīḍā bhavati tādṛśī|| 26.14||
yat kila tvaṃ mahādeva gaṇeśairvividhaiḥ śubhaiḥ|
ramase tadaniṣṭaṃ hi mama māturvṛṣadhvaja|| 26.15||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato devaḥ prahasyāha devīṃ hāsayituṃ prabhuḥ|
evam etanna saṃdehaḥ kasmānmanyurabhūt tava|| 26.16||
kṛttivāsā hyavāsā vā śmaśānanilayaśca ha|
aniketo hyaraṇyeṣu parvatānāṃ guhāsu ca|
vicarāmi gaṇairnagnairvṛto 'ambhojavilocane|| 26.17||
mā krudho devi mātustvaṃ tathyaṃ mātāvadat tava|
na hi mātṛsamo bandhurjantūnām asti śobhane|| 26.18||
devyuvāca|
na me 'asti bandhubhiḥ kiṃcit kṛtyaṃ suravareśvara|
tathā kuru mahādeva yathānyatra vasāmahe|| 26.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto deveśo devyā deveśvaraḥ prabhuḥ|
pārśvasthaṃ gaṇapaṃ prāha nikumbhaṃ nāma viśrutam|| 26.20||
gaṇeśvara nikumbha tvaṃ gatvā vārāṇasīṃ śubhām|
śūnyāṃ kuru mahābāho upāyenaiva mā balāt|| 26.21||
tatra rājā nivasati divodāsaḥ pratāpavān|
dhārmiko mama bhaktaśca mahāyogī mahābalaḥ|| 26.22||
sa tvaṃ tathā gataḥ kuryā yathāsmai nāparādhyase|
tasyaiva cāparādhena śūnyā vārāṇasī bhavet|| 26.23||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktastejasvī nikumbho gaṇasattamaḥ|
uvāca devaṃ praṇataḥ prāñjalirhṛṣitānanaḥ|| 26.24||
tathā kariṣye deveśa yathā sa hi narādhipaḥ|
bhaviṣyatyaparādhīśa tvaṃ ca tuṣṭo bhaviṣyasi|
śūnyā vārāṇasī caiva bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|| 26.25||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā nikumbho 'asau praṇamya śirasā haram|
jagāma puṇyāṃ lokeṣu purīṃ vārāṇasīṃ prabhuḥ|| 26.26||
tatrāsau darśanaṃ svapne nāpitāya dadau gaṇaḥ|
maṇḍūkākṣāya rūpaṃ ca svaṃ tasyādarśayat tadā|| 26.27||
nikumbha uvāca|
maṇḍūkākṣa nikumbho 'ahaṃ gaṇapaḥ śokanāśanaḥ|
tavānugrahakṛt prāpto yadbravīmi kuruṣva tat|| 26.28||
divodāsagṛhadvāri kuruṣva tvaṃ mamālayam|
sthāpayasva ca tatrārcāṃ madrūpasadṛśīṃ śubhām|| 26.29||
vittaṃ ca te pradāsyāmi putrān saubhāgyam eva ca|
priyatvaṃ caiva sarvatra gatiṃ cānuttamāṃ punaḥ|| 26.30||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam ukto nikumbhena nāpito nṛpatiṃ tadā|
gatvāvadaddivodāsam indravaivasvatopamam|| 26.31||
nāpita uvāca|
svāmiṃstava gṛhadvāri kariṣye gaṇapālayam|
sthāpayiṣye gaṇeśaṃ ca tanme 'anujñātum arhasi|| 26.32||
tatheti so 'apyanujñātaścakre tatra tadālayam|
pratyasthāpayadarcāṃ ca yādṛśīṃ dṛṣṭavānasau|| 26.33||
tasya pūjāṃ ca mahatīṃ prāvartayata śobhanām|
gaṇeśasya mahāsattvaḥ sa ca tāṃ pratyagṛhṇata|| 26.34||
sa tasmai karmaṇā tena vittaṃ yadyat samīhitam|
paśūṃścaiva hi putrāṃśca saubhāgyaṃ cādadat prabhuḥ|| 26.35||
tasya tāṃ vṛddhim atulāṃ nāpitasyābhivīkṣya tu|
ārirādhayiṣurlokastasya pūjāṃ cakāra ha|| 26.36||
cakruryātrāstathā kecidupavāsāṃstathāpare|
homaṃ japyaṃ tathaivānye pūjāṃ cānye varārthinaḥ|
upahārāṃstathaivānye gītanṛttaṃ tathāpare|| 26.37||
tebhyastathābhyupetebhyo nikumbhaḥ sa mahāyaśāḥ|
dadau sarvānabhiprāyān ye ye teṣām abhīpsitāḥ|| 26.38||
evaṃ taṃ kāmadaṃ jñātvā divodāso nṛpastadā|
uvāca mahiṣīṃ vyāsa kadācit putralipsayā|| 26.39||
devi sarvānabhiprāyāñjanebhyo 'ayaṃ prayacchati|
gaṇeśvaraṃ tvam apyenam apatyārthaṃ prasādaya|| 26.40||
saivam uktā tadā gatvā gaṇeśaṃ prāpya śobhanā|
uvāca bhagavan deva anapatyāham īśvara|| 26.41||
upavāsaṃ kariṣyāmi tava devābhirādhane|
tāvanna bhokṣye yāvanme varo dattastvayā prabho|| 26.42||
jāte ca putre dāsyāmi śatānāṃ daśatīrdaśa|
tvām uddiśya dvijātibhyo godhenūnāṃ gaṇeśvara|| 26.43||
tathā ghaṭasahasreṇa dadhnaścaiva ghṛtasya ca|
kṣīrasya pañcagavyasya kariṣye snapanaṃ ca te|| 26.44||
brāhmaṇānāṃ sahasrāṇāṃ śataṃ cāpi supūjitam|
purastādbhojayiṣye te putre jāte na saṃśayaḥ|| 26.45||
bahūn dāsyati rājā ca grāmān dāsyastathaiva ca|
sadā sattraṃ ca pūjāṃ ca kariṣyati tava prabho|| 26.46||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sā tam uktvā tathā vyāsa tasthau niyamam āsthitā|
sopavāsā tadā pūjāṃ mahatīṃ tasya kurvatī|| 26.47||
tāṃ tathā tiṣṭhatīṃ devaḥ provāca sa gaṇeśvaraḥ|
uttiṣṭha nāsti te putro mā khedaṃ tvaṃ vṛthā kṛthāḥ|| 26.48||
evaṃ tena gaṇeśena nikumbhena mahātmanā|
asakṛt procyamānā sā niyamādvirarāma ha|| 26.49||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ mahiṣyā sa proktaḥ svayam eva narādhipaḥ|
sadā saniyamastasthau gaṇeśasyāgrato nṛpaḥ|| 26.51||
tam apyuvāca nṛpatiṃ nikumbho niyamasthitam|
mā sthā vṛtheha nṛpate na te putraṃ dadāmyaham|| 26.52||
evam uktaḥ sa rājendro nikumbhena mahābalaḥ|
krodharaktekṣaṇaḥ prāha tam utthāya gaṇeśvaram|| 26.53||
rājovāca|
gaṇo vā tvaṃ piśāco vā bhūto vā rākṣaso 'api vā|
kṛtaghnastvaṃ na saṃdeho na tvaṃ pūjām ihārhasi|| 26.54||
mama caiva gṛhadvāri pauraiścaiva samarcitaḥ|
viṣaye mama vāsī ca na ca putraṃ prayacchasi|| 26.55||
pūjārho na bhavāṃstasmānmatto daṇḍaṃ tvam arhasi|
nṛśaṃsaścāvaliptaśca niṣṭhuro matsarānvitaḥ|| 26.56||
tato 'asya bhedayāmāsa nilayaṃ gajayūthapaiḥ|
sthaṇḍilaṃ ca babhañjāśu dadāhārcāṃ ca suprabhām|| 26.57||
nikumbho 'api kṛtārthaḥ san ākāśe saṃsthitaḥ prabhuḥ|
uvāca taṃ divodāsaṃ pradahanniva tejasā|| 26.58||
yatheṣṭaṃ samprayacchanti devā varam abhīpsitam|
na datto yadyasau kopaḥ kastatra bhavato 'abhavat|| 26.59||
yasmānmamālayo bhagnastvayā nirapakāriṇaḥ|
tasmādvarṣasahasraṃ te purī śūnyā bhaviṣyati|| 26.60||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktvā rājānaṃ nikumbhaḥ paramātmavān|
deveśāya nivedyaivaṃ tasthau pārśvagataḥ prabhoḥ|| 26.61||
rājāpi tasya vākyena tathyenārthena caiva hi|
vrīḍāṃ parāṃ samāsādya gṛhānabhyagamat tadā|| 26.62||
atha sā tena śāpena purī vārāṇasī tadā|
śūnyā samabhavat kṣipraṃ viśuddhā mṛgasevitā|| 26.63||
tāṃ tu śūnyāṃ sa vijñāya devyā saha pinākadhṛk|
sagaṇo nandinā sārdham ājagāma mahādyutiḥ|| 26.64||
sa tatra mānasaṃ divyaṃ vimānaṃ sūryavarcasam|
anaupamyaguṇaṃ devo manasaivābhinirmime|| 26.65||
na me prabhavati prajñā kṛtsnaśastannirūpaṇe|
etāvacchakyate vaktum anaupamyaguṇaṃ hi tat|| 26.66||
devodyānāni ramyāṇi nandanādyāni yāni tu|
tebhyaḥ śreṣṭhatamaṃ śrīmadudyānam asṛjat prabhuḥ|| 26.67||
tasmin vimāne girirājaputrī sarvarddhiyukte vacasām agamye|
reme navendīvaraphullanetrā devī na sasmāra vacaśca mātuḥ|| 26.68||
iti skandapurāṇe
ṣaḍ{}viṃśatimo 'adhyāyaḥ||

saptaviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha tasmin sukhāsīnau śailajāvṛṣabhadhvajau|
āsane kāñcane divye nānāratnopaśobhite|| 27.1||
athācalasutā devī sukhāsīnā vibhāvarī|
sarvalokapatiṃ prāha girīndratanayā patim|| 27.2||
bhagavan devatārighna candrāvayavabhūṣaṇa|
kathayaitanmama vibho yat tvāṃ pṛcchāmi mānada|| 27.3||
kiṃ phalaṃ tava deveśa labhante bhaktavatsala|
bhaktā ye phalam uddiśya kurvate tava kiṃcana|| 27.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam umayā proktaḥ śūlapāṇirvṛṣadhvajaḥ|
avocat sarvam avyagro devadevaḥ śubhāśubham|| 27.5||
vyāsa uvāca|
kiṃ tat sa bhagavān devaḥ prīyamāṇo mahātapāḥ|
praṇayāt sa tadā devyā pṛṣṭo 'akathayadavyayaḥ|| 27.6||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
mayāpyetat purā vyāsa pṛṣṭo nandīśvaraḥ prabhuḥ|
yathoktavān mayi brahmaṃstathā tat kathayāmi te|| 27.7||
gaṇeśānaṃ mahābhāgaṃ sūryāyutasamaprabham|
apṛccham aham avyagro nandīśvaraṃ mahādyutim|| 27.8||
īśena yat purā devyāḥ kathitaṃ gaṇasattama|
tanme brūhi yathātattvaṃ paraṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me|| 27.9||
nandīśvarovāca|
śrūyatām abhidhāsyāmi pṛcchataste mahāmune|
devadevena pārvatyā yat purā kathitaṃ hitam|| 27.10||
deva uvāca|
śrūyatām abhidhāsyāmi yanmāṃ pṛcchasi suvrate|
hitāya devi bhaktānāṃ pṛṣṭaste kathayāmi te|| 27.11||
prāsādaṃ yastu me devi śubhraṃ kuryādanindite|
vidadhāmyarjunaṃ tasya gṛhaṃ śivapure 'akṣayam|| 27.12||
vidhānena yathoktena liṅgaṃ me sthāpayecca yaḥ|
carate sa mayā sārdhaṃ nityam aṣṭaguṇānvitaḥ|| 27.13||
kāñcanaṃ tuṭimātraṃ vā yo dadyādbahu vā mama|
tasya haimavate śṛṅge dadāni gṛham uttamam|| 27.14||
yo me gāstu hiraṇyaṃ vā dadyādavimanāḥ priye|
lokān dadānyahaṃ tasmai sarvakāmasamanvitān|| 27.15||
vṛṣabhaṃ yaḥ prayaccheta śvetaṃ nīlam athāpi vā|
sa kulānām ubhayatastārayedekaviṃśatim|| 27.16||
gocarmadvayasāṃ vāpi yo me dadyādvasundharām|
sa me puraṃ samāsādya gaṇeśaiḥ saha modate|| 27.17||
yo me puṇyaphalaṃ dadyādātmanā pūrvam arjitam|
so 'anantaphalam āpnoti modate ca triviṣṭape|| 27.18||
yo 'anuyānaṃ caturdaśyāṃ kṛṣṇasya kurute mama|
rathena vṛṣayuktena mama loke sa modate|| 27.19||
manasā cintayedyaśca pūjayeyam ahaṃ haram|
aśakto nāsti me dravyaṃ yasya nityaṃ sumadhyame|| 27.21||
sa tayā śraddhayā pūto vimuktaḥ sarvapātakaiḥ|
mama lokam avāpnoti bhinne dehe na saṃśayaḥ|| 27.22||
snātvā yaḥ pūrvasaṃdhyāyāṃ sadā mām upagacchati|
sa mitraṃ yakṣarājasya yakṣo bhavati vīryavān|| 27.23||
saṃmārjanaṃ pañcaśataṃ sahasram upalepanam|
gandhāśca daśasāhasrā ānantyaṃ cārcanaṃ smṛtam|| 27.24||
abhyaṅgo 'aṣṭaśataṃ caiva snapanaṃ triśataṃ bhavet|
gandhodakaṃ pañcaśataṃ pañcagavyaṃ tathaiva ca|| 27.25||
kṣamāmi devi cāsyeha aparādhān bahūnapi|
bhasmābhiṣekam ānantyaṃ guhyaṃ caitanmamepsitam|| 27.27||
agaruṃ daśasāhasraṃ ṣaṭsahasraṃ tu candanam|
caturdaśasahasrāṇi dhūpaḥ kālāgaruḥ smṛtaḥ|| 27.28||
akṣatāstaṇḍulayavāḥ śālayo dviśatāḥ smṛtāḥ|
ānantyo gugguluścaiva sahājyena sudhūpitaḥ|| 27.29||
dve sahasre palānāṃ tu mahiṣākṣasya yo dahet|
devi saṃvatsaraṃ pūrṇaṃ sa me nandisamo bhavet|| 27.30||
ghṛtapātram asaṃkhyeyam iha pretya ca śāśvatam|
prīṇāti ca pitR̥n sarvān vimāne caiva modate|
chattraṃ dadyācca yaḥ so 'api dīpyate tejasā divi|| 27.33||
ubhe pakṣe trayodaśyām aṣṭamyāṃ copavāsikaḥ|
upatiṣṭheta māṃ bhaktyā sopahāram anindite|
dadānyasya svakaṃ lokaṃ tuṣṭo 'ahaṃ devi śāśvatam|| 27.34||
raktapītakavāsobhiḥ puṣpaiśca vividhairapi|
pūjito 'ahaṃ sadā bhaktyā putratve kalpayāmi tam|| 27.35||
ekarātraṃ ca yo martyo dīpaṃ dhārayati sthitaḥ|
sarvayajñaphalaṃ tasya dadāni śriyam eva ca|| 27.36||
mayaiva mohitāḥ sarve lokāḥ sajaḍapaṇḍitāḥ|
na māṃ paśyanti rāgāndhāstamasā bahulīkṛtāḥ|| 27.37||
dhyānino nityayuktā ye satyadharmaparāyaṇāḥ|
ekāgramanaso dāntāste māṃ paśyanti nityadā|| 27.38||
ye me bhaktāḥ sadā caiva sāṃkhyayogaviśāradāḥ|
sarvaṃ paśyanti ca mayi māṃ ca sarvatra yogataḥ|| 27.39||
trī/llokān samatikramya brahmalokaṃ tathaiva ca|
gacchanti mama te lokaṃ tamo bhittvā sudurbhidam|| 27.40||
na śakyo 'asmi tapoyuktairdraṣṭuṃ munigaṇairapi|
dhyānino nityayuktāśca devi paśyanti māṃ budhāḥ|| 27.41||
yāni lokeṣu tīrthāni devatāyatanāni ca|
pādayostāni suśroṇi sadā saṃnihitāni me|| 27.42||
mayyarpitamanā nityaṃ tathā madbhāvabhāvitaḥ|
mamaiva sa prabhāvena sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 27.43||
sarvathā vartamāno 'api devi yo māṃ sadā smaret|
kalmaṣeṇa na yujyeta naraḥ kartā kadācana|| 27.44||
sarvāvastho 'api pāpātmā jñānaniṣṭhena cetasā|
yo 'abhyarcayati māṃ nityaṃ sa mamātmasamo bhavet|| 27.45||
ṣaḍaṅgena ca yogena yo mām arcayata sadā|
praviśeta sa māṃ kṣipram atra nāsti vicāraṇā|| 27.46||
yo 'apyasajjanarato viyonijaḥ pātakairapi samanvitaḥ sadā|
so 'api madgatamanā madarpaṇo yāti devi gatim apratarkitām|| 27.47||
iti skandapurāṇe saptaviṃśatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ||

aṣṭāviṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato vyāsa punardevī patiṃ vratapatiṃ śubhā|
apṛcchadvratasambaddhaṃ phalaṃ phalaśatārcitā|| 28.1||
vratānāṃ phalam alpaṃ vā mahadvā yat trilokapa|
vrataṃ bhavati yādṛgvā tat prabrūhi maheśvara|| 28.2||
deva uvāca|
mahāphalaṃ yadbhavati yaccāpyalpaphalaṃ śubhe|
vrataṃ yādṛk ca yat proktaṃ tacchṛṇuṣva-m-anindite|| 28.3||
caturdaśyāṃ tathāṣṭamyām ubhayoḥ pakṣayoḥ śuciḥ|
saṃvatsaram abhuñjānaḥ śānto dānto jitendriyaḥ|| 28.4||
sattrayājiphalaṃ yacca satyavāgṛtugāminām|
taccaiva phalam āpnoti yamaṃ caiva na paśyati|| 28.5||
śayyāsanasthaḥ strīmadhye ratiraktaḥ sukhe rataḥ|
sa tapyati ā nakhāgrebhyo nityaṃ yo māṃ samāśritaḥ|| 28.6||
madbhaktastapasā yukto mām eva pratipadyate|
lokāstasyākṣayā devi yadyapi syāt supāpakṛt|| 28.7||
pṛthivībhājane bhuṅkte nityaṃ parvasu yo naraḥ|
sa trirātraphalaṃ devi ahorātreṇa vindati|| 28.8||
saṃvatsaraṃ tu yo bhuṅkte nityam eva hyatandritaḥ|
nivedya pitṛdevebhyaḥ pṛthivyām ekarāḍbhavet|| 28.9||
navamī aṣṭamī caiva paurṇamāsī trayodaśī|
yo bhuṅkte devi naiteṣu saṃyatastu naraḥ samām|| 28.10||
gāṇapatyaṃ sa labhate niḥsapatnam anindite|
bhūtānāṃ dayitaścaiva divyaṃ rūpaṃ bibharti ca|| 28.11||
śrīvatsaṃ yaśca piṣṭena dadyāddhemaphalaṃ śubham|
kiret kṛṣṇatilāṃścātra taṇḍulākṣatam eva ca|
phalaiśca vividhākārairyathālabdhai rasānvitaiḥ|| 28.12||
sa vai varṣasahasrāṇi dviṣaṣṭiṃ divi modate|
divyarūpadharaḥ śrīmān devataiḥ saha nityaśaḥ|| 28.13||
hariberamayīṃ yo me dadyāt pratikṛtiṃ svakām|
sarvagandharasairyuktāṃ niryāsaiśca susaṃskṛtām|| 28.14||
pārśveṣu haritālaṃ ca kṛṣṇāgarumanaḥśilām|
candanaṃ caiva dadyādvai yathāsaṃkhyena pūjitam|| 28.16||
tasya puṇyaphalaṃ devi śṛṇu yanmattakāśini|
sarvavyādhivinirmuktastathā niṣkalmaṣaśca ha|| 28.17||
varṣakoṭiśatānyaṣṭau divi bhuktvā mahat sukham|
iha loke sukhī jāto mām eva pratipadyate|| 28.18||
ratnāvaliṃ tu yo dadyādbrāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo 'atha viṭ|
śūdraḥ strī vā sa me loke matsaukhyaṃ prāpnute param|| 28.19||
siddhārthakairathārghārthaṃ daive pitrye 'athavā punaḥ|
triṃśadvarṣasahasrāṇi tarpayet sa pitR̥nnapi|| 28.20||
ṛṣīṃśca sarvadevāṃśca rūpaṃ cāpnoti puṣkalam|
manvantaraṃ ca goloke gokanyābhiḥ sa pūjyate|| 28.21||
sarve devāstathā viṣṇurbrahmā ṛṣaya eva ca|
kurvantyarghe hi sāṃnidhyaṃ tebhyastadviddhi niḥsṛtam|| 28.22||
guhyam etat paraṃ devi yo vetti sa mahātapāḥ|
tasya prabhāvājjāyeta dhanavān priyadarśanaḥ|
prajñārūpaguṇairyuktaḥ saṃvatsaraśatāyutam|| 28.23||
kṣīreṇa yo māṃ satataṃ snāpayeta trirudyataḥ|
aparādhasahasraṃ tu kṣame tasyāham antaśaḥ|| 28.24||
yaśca tat snapanaṃ paśyet sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
mānasasya ca jāpyasya sahasrasya phalaṃ labhet|| 28.25||
saṃvatsaraṃ tu yaḥ kuryāt kṣīreṇa snapanaṃ śuciḥ|
gāṇapatyaṃ sa labhate vallabhatvaṃ ca nityaśaḥ|| 28.26||
sarpiṣā yo mamābhyaṅgaṃ karotyavimanā naraḥ|
dvisāhasrasya jāpyasya mānasasya phalaṃ labhet|| 28.27||
abhigamyaśca devānāṃ sa bhaveta narottamaḥ|
niṣkāṇāṃ ca suvarṇasya sahasrasya phalaṃ labhet|| 28.28||
saṃmārjanaṃ ca yaḥ kuryāt saṃvatsaram anuvrataḥ|
vitarāmi śubhaṃ lokaṃ nityaṃ tasya dhruvaṃ śivam|
sarvalokakṣaye tasya na kṣayo bhavatīśvari|| 28.29||
liṅgapūjāṃ tu yaḥ kuryānmama devi dṛḍhavrataḥ|
śataṃ varṣasahasrāṇi divyāni divi modate|| 28.30||
caturṇāṃ puṣpajātīnāṃ gandham āghrāti śaṃkaraḥ|
arkasya karavīrasya bilvasya ca bukasya ca|
suvarṇaniṣkaṃ puṣpe tu sarvasmin devi kathyate|| 28.31||
sahasre tvarkapuṣpāṇāṃ datte yat kathyate phalam|
ekasmin karavīrasya datte puṣpe hi tat phalam|| 28.32||
karavīrasahasrasya bhaveddattasya yat phalam|
tadekasya tu padmasya dattasya phalam ucyate|| 28.33||
padmānāṃ tu sahasrasya mama dattasya yat phalam|
tat phalaṃ labhate pattre datte bilvasya śobhane|| 28.34||
bilvapattrasahasre tu datte me yat phalaṃ smṛtam|
bukapuṣpe tadekasmin mama datte labhet phalam|| 28.35||
bukapuṣpasahasrasya mama dattasya yat phalam|
puṣpe datte tadekasmi/llabheddhuttūrakasya tu|| 28.36||
nirmālyaṃ yo hi me nityaṃ śirasā dhārayiṣyati|
aśucirbhinnamaryādo naraḥ pāpasamanvitaḥ|| 28.37||
svairī caiva tathāyukto niyamaiśca bahiṣkṛtaḥ|
narake sa patedghore tiryagyonau ca sambhavet|| 28.38||
brahmacārī śucirbhūtvā nirmālyaṃ yastu dhārayet|
tasya pāpam ahaṃ śīghraṃ nāśayāmi mahāvrate|| 28.39||
dīpamālāṃ tu yaḥ kuryāt kārttike māsi vai mama|
avasāne ca dīpānāṃ brāhmaṇāṃstarpayecchuciḥ|
gāṇapatyaṃ sa labhate dīpyate ca raviryathā|| 28.40||
dadyāt kṛṣṇatilāṃścaiva saha siddhārthakāṃśca ha|
yo me devi sadā mūrdhni sa me nandisamo bhavet|| 28.41||
ye hi siddhārthakāḥ proktāstathā kṛṣṇatilāśca ye|
sarve te tvanmayā devi guhyam etanmayeritam|| 28.42||
citro nāma gaṇo mahyaṃ tena sārdhaṃ sa modate|
sarvasampralaye caiva prāpte trailokyasaṃkṣaye|
tyaktvā sarvāṇi duḥkhāni mām eva pratipadyate|| 28.43||
na tuṣyāmyarcito 'arcāyāṃ tathā devi nagātmaje|
liṅge 'arcite yathātyarthaṃ parituṣyāmi pārvati|| 28.44||
sarvendriyaprasakto vā yukto vā sarvapātakaiḥ|
sa prayāti divaṃ devi liṅgaṃ yo 'arcayatīha me|| 28.45||
tyaktvā sarvāṇi pāpāni nirdvandvo dagdhakilbiṣaḥ|
madāśīrmannamaskāro mām eva pratipadyate|| 28.46||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato bhagavatī bhūyaḥ patiṃ sarvajagatpatim|
apṛcchat puṣpyamāṇāsyā kena tvaṃ deva tuṣyasi|| 28.47||
tataḥ prahasamānāsyaḥ sarvalokeśvareśvaraḥ|
vacaḥ provāca bhagavā/llokānāṃ hitakāmyayā|| 28.48||
deva uvāca|
śṛṇu devi yathātattvaṃ yena yānti śubhāṃ gatim|
trailokye jantavaḥ sarve madbhaktā ye śubhānane|| 28.49||
yat tat parataraṃ guhyaṃ tat sarvaṃ tvayi tiṣṭhati|
yo hi tattvena tadveda saṃsārādvipramucyate|| 28.50||
na ca prakāśayedguhyaṃ nāma te kīrtayennaraḥ|
sadā sarvasahetyevaṃ prātaḥ prāñjalirutthitaḥ|| 28.51||
tasmācca kīrtanāt pāpaṃ sarvam eva vinirdahet|
yaśaḥ kīrtiṃ ca samprāpya rudraloke mahīyate|| 28.52||
sarvamālyāni yo dadyāt sarvamūrtiṣu nityaśaḥ|
mantreṇa vidhivaccaiva tasya puṇyaphalaṃ mahat|| 28.53||
mantraḥ|
sarvagāya sureśāya sarvadevamayāya ca|
namo bhagavate caiva guhyāguhyāya vai sadā|| 28.54||
somāya bhūtanāthāya bhāvanāya bhavāya ca|
sarvaguhyāya vai svāhā devaguhyamayāya ca|| 28.55||
sarvaguhyamayo mantraḥ svāhā somāya caiva ha|
kaṭaṃkaṭāyaiva svāhā svāhā devāya śuṣmiṇe|| 28.56||
puṣpāṇyetena mantreṇa yo me nityaṃ nivedayet|
sahasraṃ tena jāpyasya mānasasya kṛtaṃ bhavet|| 28.57||
athāñjalim amāvāsyāṃ susampūrṇāṃ samāhitaḥ|
tilānāṃ caiva kṛṣṇānāṃ sarṣapāṇāṃ ca pārvati|
arcayitvā yathānyāyaṃ yathālābhaṃ prayacchati|| 28.58||
idaṃ ca vacanaṃ brūyāt sūryeti ca mameti ca|
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ svargalokaṃ vrajennaraḥ|| 28.59||
arcayitvā ca māṃ devi brāhmaṇān na ca tarpayet|
na tatphalam avāpnoti nāhaṃ tuṣyāmi tasya vai|| 28.60||
arcayitvā dvijān māṃ ca yo me nāmāni kīrtayet|
caturdaśyām athāṣṭamyāṃ pakṣayorubhayorapi|
so 'api devi prapaśyenmāṃ viyoniṃ na sa gacchati|| 28.61||
vāmadeva sudeveti hara gupteti vā punaḥ|
umāpate nīlakaṇṭha śānta śrīkaṇṭha gopate|| 28.62||
śarva bhīma paśupate śaṃkarogra bhaveti ca|
mahādeveti cāpyanyannāma guhyaṃ prakīrtayet|
sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyeta divi devaiśca pūjyate|| 28.63||
eteṣām ekam api yaḥ kathayedvā paṭheta vā|
sa dehapaddhatiṃ bhittvā mām eva pratipadyate|
evaṃ sarvapraṇāmena yanmayā parikīrtitam|| 28.64||
amāvāsyāṃ tu yo nityaṃ saghṛtaṃ guggulaṃ dahet|
kṣīreṇa caiva saṃmiśraṃ guhyam etanmama priye|
so 'acyutaṃ sthānam āpnoti matprasādānna saṃśayaḥ|| 28.65||
idaṃ ca paramaṃ guhyaṃ yo me devi nivedayet|
arkaparṇapuṭaṃ pūrṇaṃ ghṛtasya madhunā saha|
nivedya vidhivadbhaktyā sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 28.66||
imāni ca mahābhāge yo me nāmāni kīrtayet|
śmaśānanilayo nagno bhasmaśāyī yatavrataḥ|| 28.67||
vāmadevaḥ praśāntaśca stabdhaśephastrilocanaḥ|
avasavyapriyaḥ savyo bahurūpo 'antakāntakṛt|| 28.68||
purāṇaḥ puruhūtaśca mṛtyormṛtyurjitendriyaḥ|
anindriyo 'atīndriyaśca sarvabhūtahṛdi sthitaḥ|| 28.69||
saṃsāracakrī yogātmā kāpālī diṇḍireva ca|
mahādevo mahādevo mahādeveti caiva hi|| 28.70||
japedetanniyamavān śṛṇuyādvāpi nityaśaḥ|
sa dehabhedam āsādya yogātmā gaṇapo bhavet|| 28.71||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
nāśubhāya na pāpāya nānṛtāya kadācana|
śrāvayedbhaktimān puṇyaṃ nāpetāya kadācana|| 28.72||
dhanyaṃ yaśasyam āyuṣyaṃ śāntivṛddhikaraṃ śubham|
pūtaṃ pavitraṃ paramaṃ maṅgalānāṃ ca maṅgalam|
śrotavyaṃ na ca sarveṇa tathā deyaṃ na kasyacit|| 28.73||
iti skandapurāṇe īśvarapūjā nāmāṣṭāviṃśatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|

ūnatriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
evaṃ kālena samprāpya vārāṇasyāṃ niketanam|
jagataḥ pitarau devau cakratuḥ kim ataḥ param|| 29.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devo devīṃ himavataḥ sutām|
uvāca devi paśyāma udyānaṃ yadi rocate|| 29.2||
devyuvāca|
evaṃ bhavatu deveśa yathāttha tvaṃ vṛṣadhvaja|
na hi me 'anyatra gantavyam udyānāt parato hara|| 29.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
saha devyā tato vyāsa vārāṇasyāṃ vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
devodyānadidṛkṣārthaṃ vicacāra samantataḥ|| 29.4||
pūrvasmin sa diśābhāge devyā devaḥ pinākadhṛk|
udyānaṃ darśayāmāsa nānākusumaśobhitam|| 29.5||
campakāśokapuṃnāgapriyaṅgūcūtasaṃkulam|
bilvārjunakadambaiśca nyagrodhodumbarairapi|| 29.6||
gandhavadbhiśca kusumairjātīkesaraketakaiḥ|
ramyaiḥ surabhipuṣpaiśca ṣaṭpadavrātasevitaiḥ|
saṃyuktaṃ sarvataḥ śrīmadvanaṃ vaibhrājasaṃnibham|| 29.7||
sa tadudyānam āsādya devīm āha jagatpatiḥ|
asmin deśe purā devi tiṣṭhato mama śobhane|| 29.8||
ūrdhvaṃ golokasaṃsthānāṃ gavāṃ vatsaiḥ svayaṃbhuvaiḥ|
pīyatīnāṃ payo vegāt phenaṃ mūrdhni samāpatat|| 29.9||
tato mayordhvaṃ dṛṣṭāstu gāvastāḥ somapārśvagāḥ|
tatastāḥ prekṣitāstatra mayā gāvastadābhavan|
tejasā dahyamānāstu naikavarṇā bhṛśārditāḥ|| 29.10||
gāvaḥ pūrvam imā devi āsan kapilavarṇajāḥ|
naikavarṇāstadābhūvan yadā samprekṣitā mayā|| 29.11||
tāsāṃ śaraṇyatāṃ yātvā tābhirmām eva śailaje|
āśritaḥ soma āgatya saha gobhirna tāstyajat|| 29.12||
arditābhistadā gobhirbrahmā mām abravīt tataḥ|
prasādaṃ kuru deveśa surabhīstejasā tava|
na naśyanti yathā sadyastathā sarvasurārcita|| 29.13||
tato 'aham āsthito devi sthāne 'asmin svayam eva tu|
goprekṣaka iti khyātaḥ saṃstutaḥ sarvadevataiḥ|| 29.14||
goprekṣeśvaram āgatya dṛṣṭvā cārcya ca mānavaḥ|
na durgatim avāpnoti kalmaṣaiśca vimucyate|| 29.15||
tatastā dahyamānāstu prasanne surabhī mayi|
hrade 'asmin peturabhyetya śāntāstā vibabhustadā|
kapilāhrada ityevaṃ tadāprabhṛti kathyate|| 29.16||
atrāpi svayam evāhaṃ vṛṣadhvaja iti śrutaḥ|
sāṃnidhyaṃ kṛtavān devi sa cāyaṃ dṛśyatāṃ sthitaḥ|| 29.17||
kapilāhradatīrthe 'asmin snātvā nānyamanā naraḥ|
vṛṣadhvajam imaṃ dṛṣṭvā sarvayajñaphalaṃ labhet|| 29.18||
salokatāṃ mṛtaścāpi arcayitvā tu mām iha|
labhate dehabhede tu gaṇatvaṃ cātidurlabham|| 29.19||
asminnapi pradeśe tu tā gāvo brahmaṇā svayam|
śāntyarthaṃ sarvalokānāṃ sarvā dugdhāḥ payomṛtam|| 29.20||
tāsāṃ kṣīreṇa saṃjātaṃ hradam etanmanoharam|
bhadradoham iti khyātaṃ puṇyaṃ devavanaṃ śubham|| 29.21||
sarvairdevairahaṃ devi asmin deśe prasāditaḥ|
gacchopaśamam īśeti upaśāntaśivastataḥ|| 29.22||
sthito bhūtvāham atrasthaḥ puṇyam asyāpi darśanam|
dṛṣṭvainaṃ prayato martyaḥ svargalokam avāpnuyāt|| 29.23||
atrāhaṃ brahmaṇānīya sthāpitaḥ parameṣṭhinā|
brahmaṇaścāpi saṃgṛhya viṣṇunā sthāpitaḥ punaḥ|| 29.24||
brahmaṇā sa tato viṣṇuḥ proktaḥ saṃvignacetasā|
mayānītam idaṃ liṅgaṃ kasmāt sthāpitavānasi|| 29.25||
tam uvāca punarviṣṇurbrahmāṇaṃ kupitānanam|
rudradeve mamātyantaṃ purā bhaktirmahattarā|| 29.26||
mayaiṣa sthāpitastena nāmnā tava bhaviṣyati|
hiraṇyagarbha ityevaṃ tato 'atrāhaṃ samāsthitaḥ|
dṛṣṭvainam api deveśaṃ mama lokaṃ vrajennaraḥ|| 29.27||
punaścāpi tato brahmā mama liṅgam imaṃ śubhe|
sthāpayāmāsa vidhivadbhaktyā paramayā yutaḥ|
svarlīneśvara ityevam atrāhaṃ svayam āsthitaḥ|| 29.28||
svasmin paratare līnaḥ pradhāne mama kāraṇe|
tasmāt svarlīna ityevaṃ guhyaṃ kṣetraṃ mama smṛtam|| 29.29||
prāṇāniha narastyaktvā na punarjāyate kvacit|
ānantyā sā gatistasya yogināṃ caiva sā smṛtā|| 29.30||
asminnapi mayā deśe daityo devatakaṇṭakaḥ|
vyāghrarūpaṃ samāsthāya nihato darpito balī|| 29.31||
vyāghreśvarastataḥ khyāto nityam atrāham āsthitaḥ|
na punardurgatiṃ yāti dṛṣṭvainam amareśvaram|| 29.32||
utpalo vidalaścaiva yau daityau brahmaṇā purā|
strīvadhyau darpitau sṛṣṭau tvayaiva nihatau śubhe|
sāvajñaṃ geṇḍukenātra tasyedaṃ cihnam āsthitam|| 29.33||
ādāvatrāham āgatya āsthito gaṇapaiḥ saha|
jyeṣṭhaṃ sthānam idaṃ tasmādetanme puṇyadarśanam|| 29.34||
dṛṣṭvemaṃ mama liṅgaṃ tu jyeṣṭhasthānasamāśritam|
na śocati punarmartyaḥ saṃsiddho mṛtyujanmanī|| 29.35||
samantāddevataiḥ sarvairliṅgāni sthāpitāni ha|
dṛṣṭvā tu niyato martyo dehabhede gaṇo bhavet|| 29.36||
idānīm aham āgatya svayam eva yataḥ sthitam|
na ca muktaṃ mayā yasmādavimuktam idaṃ tataḥ|
kṣetraṃ vārāṇasī puṇyā muktidaṃ sambhaviṣyati|| 29.37||
avimukteśvaraṃ māṃ vai yo 'atra drakṣyati mānavaḥ|
gāṇapatyā gatistasya yatra tatra mṛtasya ha|
prāṇāniha tu saṃnyasya yāsyate muktim uttamām|| 29.38||
pitrā te girirājena purā himavatā svayam|
mama priyam idaṃ sthānaṃ jñātvā liṅgaṃ pratiṣṭhitam|| 29.39||
śaileśvaram iti khyātaṃ dṛśyatām idam āsthitam|
dṛṣṭvedaṃ manujo devi na durgatim anuvrajet|| 29.40||
nadī vārāṇasī ceyaṃ puṇyā pāpapramocanī|
kṣetram etadalaṃkṛtya jāhnavyā saha saṃgatā|| 29.41||
sthāpitaṃ saṃgame cāsmin brahmaṇā liṅgam uttamam|
saṃgameśvaram ityevaṃ khyātaṃ jagati dṛśyatām|| 29.42||
saṃgame devanadyostu yaḥ snātvā manujaḥ śuciḥ|
arcayet saṃgameśānaṃ tasya janmabhayaṃ kutaḥ|| 29.43||
idam anyadbṛhat kṣetraṃ nivāsaṃ yogināṃ param|
kṣetramadhye ca yatrāhaṃ svayaṃ bhūtvā samāsthitaḥ|
madhyameśvara ityevaṃ khyātaḥ sarvasurāsuraiḥ|| 29.44||
siddhānāṃ sthānam etaddhi madīyavratacāriṇām|
yogināṃ mokṣalipsūnāṃ janmamṛtyujitātmanām|
dṛṣṭvedaṃ madhyameśānaṃ janma prati na śocati|| 29.45||
sthāpitaṃ liṅgam etacca śukreṇa tava sūnunā|
nāmnā śukreśvaraṃ nāma sarvasiddhāmarārcitam|| 29.46||
dṛṣṭvedaṃ mānavaḥ sadyo muktaḥ syāt sarvakilbiṣaiḥ|
mṛtaśca na punarjanma saṃsāre tu labhennaraḥ|| 29.47||
purā jambukarūpeṇa asurā devakaṇṭakāḥ|
brahmaṇo 'atha varaṃ labdhvā gomāyuvadhaśaṅkitāḥ|| 29.48||
nihatā himavatputri jambukeśastato hyaham|
abhavaṃ jagati khyātaḥ surāsuranamaskṛtaḥ|
dṛṣṭvainam api deveśaṃ sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt|| 29.49||
grahaiḥ śukrapurogaiśca etāni sthāpitāni hi|
paśya liṅgāni puṇyāni sarvakāmapradāni tu|| 29.50||
evam etāni puṇyāni mannivāsāni pārvati|
kathitāni tava kṣetre guhyaṃ cānyadidaṃ śṛṇu|| 29.51||
krośaṃ krośaṃ caturdikṣu kṣetram etat prakīrtitam|
yojanaṃ viddhi cārvaṅgi mṛtyukāle 'amṛtapradam|| 29.52||
}$\versenum=52$
mahālayagiristhāne kedāre ca vyavasthitam
gaṇatvaṃ labhate dṛṣṭvā kṣetre 'asmin mokṣa-m-āpyate|| 29.53||
gāṇapatyapadāt tasmādyataḥ sā muktiruttamā|
tato mahālayāt tasmāt kedārānmadhyamādapi|
smṛtaṃ puṇyatamaṃ kṣetram avimuktam idaṃ śubhe|| 29.54||
kedāramadhyame sthāne sthānaṃ caiva mahālayam|
mama puṇyāni bhūrloke tebhyaḥ śreṣṭhatamaṃ tvidam|| 29.55||
yataḥ sṛṣṭāni lokāni tataḥ kṣetram idaṃ śubham|
kadācinna mayā muktam avimuktaṃ tato 'abhavat|| 29.56||
avimukteśvaraṃ liṅgaṃ mama dṛṣṭveha mānavaḥ|
sadyaḥ pāpavinirmuktaḥ paśupāśairvimucyate|| 29.57||
śaileśaṃ saṃgameśaṃ ca svarlīnaṃ madhyameśvaram|
hiraṇyagarbham īśānaṃ goprekṣaṃ savṛṣadhvajam|| 29.58||
upaśāntaśivaṃ caiva jyeṣṭhasthānanivāsinam|
śukreśvaraṃ ca vikhyātaṃ vyāghreśaṃ jambukeśvaram|
dṛṣṭvā na jāyate martyaḥ saṃsāre duḥkhasāgare|| 29.59||
evam uktvā mahādevo diśaḥ sarvā vyalokayat|
vilokya saṃsthite paścāddevadeve maheśvare|| 29.60||
akasmādabhavat sarvaṃ taddeśaṃ jvalitaṃ yathā|
savidyutstanitāghoṣaṃ sūryāyutaśatoditam|| 29.61||
tejobhirekataḥ pūrṇaṃ vahnibhāskarayoriva|
tataḥ pāśupatāḥ siddhā bhasmābhyaṅgasitaprabhāḥ|| 29.62||
yogīśvarā mahātmānastathā vaitānikavratāḥ|
avyaktaliṅginaścaiva śivayogojjvalaprabhāḥ|
bahavaḥ sahasopetya namaścakrurmaheśvaram|| 29.63||
punarnirīkṣya deveśaṃ dhyānayogaṃ ca kṛtsnaśaḥ|
tasthurātmānam ādhāya līyamānā iveśvare|| 29.64||
sthitānāṃ sa tathā teṣāṃ devadeva umāpatiḥ|
saṃcintya paramāṃ mūrtiṃ babhūva puruṣaḥ prabhuḥ|| 29.65||
tasya tāṃ paramāṃ mūrtim āsthitasya jagatprabhoḥ|
na śaśāka vapurdraṣṭuṃ hṛṣṭaromā girīndrajā|| 29.67||
tatastatsṛṣṭam ātmānaṃ buddhvā sā prakṛtisthitam|
prakṛtermūrtim āsthāya yogena paramātmikā|
taṃ śaśāka vapurdraṣṭuṃ puruṣasya parātmanaḥ|| 29.68||
tataste layam ādhāya yoginaḥ puruṣasya tu|
viviśurhṛdayaṃ sarve dagdhasaṃsārabījinaḥ|| 29.69||
anugṛhya tataḥ sarvān tān siddhān yatipuṃgavān|
nīlalohitamūrtisthaṃ punaścakre vapuḥ śubham|| 29.70||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā śailajā prāha hṛṣṭasarvatanūruhā|
stunvantī caraṇau gatvā ka ime bhagavanniti|| 29.71||
tām uvāca suraśreṣṭhastadā devīṃ girīndrajām|
madīyaṃ vratam āśritya bhaktimadbhirdvijottamaiḥ|
yairyairyoga ihābhyastasteṣām ekena janmanā|| 29.72||
kṣetrasyāsya prabhāveṇa bhaktyā ca mama bhāvataḥ|
anugraho mayā hyevaṃ kriyate muktidaḥ sadā|| 29.73||
tasmādidaṃ mahat kṣetraṃ brahmādyaiḥ sevyate mama|
śrutimadbhiśca viprendraiḥ saṃsiddhaiśca tapasvibhiḥ|| 29.74||
pratimāsam athāṣṭamyāṃ pratimāsaṃ caturdaśīm|
ubhayoḥ pakṣayordevi vārāṇasyāṃ mamāspade|| 29.75||
śaśibhānūparāge ca kārttikyāṃ tu viśeṣataḥ|
sarvaparvasu puṇyeṣu viṣuveṣvayaneṣu ca|| 29.76||
pṛthivyāṃ sarvatīrthāni vārāṇasyāṃ tu jāhnavīm|
uttarapravahāṃ puṇyāṃ mama maulivinirgatām|| 29.77||
pituste girirājācca srutāṃ himavataḥ śubhām|
bhajante sarvato 'abhyetya tāñchṛṇuṣva varānane|| 29.78||
saṃnihityā kurukṣetraṃ sārdhaṃ tīrthaśataistathā|
puṣkaraṃ naimiśaṃ caiva prayāgaṃ sapṛthūdakam|| 29.79||
sandhyā saptaṛcaṃ caiva sarvā nadyaḥ sarāṃsi ca|
samudrāḥ sapta caivātra devatīrthāni kṛtsnaśaḥ|
bhāgīrathīṃ sameṣyanti sarvaparvasu kāśigām|| 29.80||
avimukteśvaraṃ māṃ ca kāśīstham acalātmaje|
pṛthivyāṃ yāni puṇyāni mahyam āyatanāni ca|
praviśanti sadābhyetya puṇyaṃ parvasu parvasu|| 29.81||
kedāre caiva yalliṅgaṃ yacca liṅgaṃ mahālaye|
madhyameśvarasaṃsthaṃ ca tathā paśupatīśvaram|| 29.82||
śaṅkukarṇeśvaraṃ caiva gokarṇe ca tathā hyubhau|
drimicaṇḍeśvaraṃ caiva bhadreśvara tathaiva ca|| 29.83||
sthāneśvaram athaikāmraṃ kāleśvaram ajeśvaram|
bhairaveśvaram īśānaṃ tathā kārohaṇāsthitam|| 29.84||
yāni cānyāni puṇyāni sthānāni mama bhūtale|
tāni sarvāṇyaśeṣeṇa kāśipuryāṃ viśanti mām|| 29.85||
sarvaparvasu puṇyeṣu guhyaṃ caitadudāhṛtam|
teneha labhyate jantorvipannasyāmṛtaṃ padam|| 29.86||
snātasya caiva gaṅgāyāṃ dṛṣṭena ca mayā śubhe|
sarvayajñaphalaistulyam iṣṭaiḥ śatasahasraśaḥ|
sadya eva-m-avāpnoti kiṃ nvataḥ param asti vai|| 29.87||
sarvāyatanamukhyānāṃ divi bhūmau giriṣvapi|
nātaḥ parataraṃ devi budhyasvāstīti kṛtsnaśaḥ|| 29.88||
brahmārkavaiśvānaraśakracandrairjaleśavittādhipavāyubhiśca|
gandharvayakṣoragasiddhasaṃghaiḥ sārdhaṃ sadā sevitam etadagryam|| 29.89||
sthānaṃ mamedaṃ himaśailaputri guhyaṃ sadā kṣetram idaṃ supuṇyam|
vimokṣasaṃsiddhiphalapradaṃ hi prabuddhatattvā yatayo vadanti|| 29.90||
kṣetre 'asmin nivasanti ye sukṛtino bhaktāḥ sadā māṃ narāḥ
evam etat suvistīrṇaṃ nānādrumalatākulam|
jāhnavyālaṃkṛtaṃ puṇyaṃ kṣetraṃ guhyatamaṃ mama|| 29.92||
bhāgīrathīm ihāsādya vārāṇasyāṃ mamāspade|
aśvamedhaśataṃ prāpya brahmalokaṃ ca gacchati|| 29.93||
nātaḥ puṇyatamaṃ devi nāto guhyatamaṃ kvacit|
nātaḥ śubhataraṃ kiṃcinnātaḥ priyataraṃ mama|| 29.94||
kṣetraṃ mamedaṃ surasiddhajuṣṭaṃ samprāpya martyaḥ sukṛtaprabhāvāt|
khyāto bhavet sarvasurāsurāṇāṃ mṛtaśca yāyāt paramaṃ padaṃ tam|| 29.95||

triṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan piṅgalaḥ kena gaṇatvaṃ samupāgataḥ|
annadatvaṃ ca samprāpto vārāṇasyāṃ mahādyutiḥ|| 30.1||
kṣetrapālaḥ kathaṃ jātaḥ priyatvaṃ ca kathaṃ gataḥ|
etadicchāmi kathitaṃ śrotuṃ brahmasuta tvayā|| 30.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vyāsa yathā lebhe gaṇeśatvaṃ sa piṅgalaḥ|
annadatvaṃ ca lokānāṃ sthānaṃ vārāṇasīṃ ca hi|| 30.3||
pūrṇabhadrasutaḥ śrīmān āsīdyakṣaḥ pratāpavān|
harikeśa iti khyāto brahmaṇyo dhārmikaśca ha|| 30.4||
tasya janmaprabhṛtyeva śarve bhaktiranuttamā|
tadāśīstannamaskārastanniṣṭhastatparāyaṇaḥ|| 30.5||
āsīnaśca śayānaśca gacchaṃstiṣṭhannanuvrajan|
bhuñjāno 'atha piban vāpi rudram evānvacintayat|| 30.6||
tam evaṃ yuktamanasaṃ pūrṇabhadraḥ pitābravīt|
na tvā putram ahaṃ manye durjāto yastvam anyathā|| 30.7||
na hi yakṣakulīnānām etadvṛttaṃ bhavatyuta|
guhyakā vata yūyaṃ vai svabhāvāt krūracetasaḥ|
kravyādāścaiva kiṃbhakṣā hiṃsāśīlāśca putraka|| 30.8||
maivaṃ kārṣīrna no vṛttirevaṃ dṛṣṭā mahātmanām|
svayambhuvā yathā sṛṣṭā saiva vṛttiḥ praśasyate|| 30.9||
harikeśa uvāca|
duṣṭā caivāpraśastā ca garhitā sādhubhiḥ sadā|
vṛttiḥ svayambhuvā sṛṣṭā tyaktavyā yadi no bhavet|
āśramāntarajaṃ karma na kuryurgṛhiṇastataḥ|| 30.10||
hitvā manuṣyabhāvaṃ ca karmabhirvividhaiśca ha|
devatvaṃ no vimārgeyurmānuṣyāṃ jātim eva ca|| 30.11||
atha cedvihitaṃ teṣāṃ karma tatprāptisaṃśritam|
mamāpi vihitaṃ paśya karmaitannātra saṃśayaḥ|| 30.12||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktaḥ putreṇa pūrṇabhadraḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca niṣkrama kṣipraṃ gaccha tvaṃ yatra rocate|| 30.13||
tataḥ sa nirgatastyaktvā gṛhasambandhibāndhavān|
vārāṇasīṃ samāsādya tapastepe suduścaram|| 30.14||
sthāṇubhūto hyanimiṣaḥ śuṣkakāṣṭhopalopamaḥ|
saṃniyamyendriyagrāmam avātiṣṭhata niścalaḥ|| 30.15||
atha tasyaivam aniśaṃ tatparasya tadāśiṣaḥ|
sahasram ekaṃ varṣāṇāṃ divyam abhyativartata|| 30.16||
valmīkena samākrānto bhakṣyamāṇaḥ pipīlikaiḥ|
vajrasūcīmukhairvyāsa vidhyamānastathaiva ca|| 30.17||
nirmāṃsarudhiratvak ca kundaśaṅkhendusaprabhaḥ|
asthiśeṣo 'abhavat sarvo devaścainam amanyata|| 30.18||
etasminnantare devī vyajñāpayata śaṃkaram|
udyānaṃ punarevedaṃ draṣṭum icchāmi sarvada|| 30.19||
kṣetrasya caiva māhātmyaṃ śrotuṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me|
yataśca priyam etat te yaccāsya phalam uttamam|| 30.20||
iti vijñāpito devaḥ pārvatyā bhuvaneśvaraḥ|
sarvaṃ pṛṣṭaṃ yathānyāyam ākhyātum upacakrame|| 30.21||
nirjagāma ca deveśaḥ pārvatyā saha śaṃkaraḥ|
udyānaṃ darśayāmāsa devyā devaḥ pinākadhṛk|| 30.22||
praphullanānāvidhagulmaśobhitaṃ latāpratānāvanataṃ manoharam|
virūḍhapuṣpaiḥ paritaḥ priyaṅgubhiḥ supuṣpitaiḥ kaṇṭakitaiśca ketakaiḥ|| 30.23||
tamālagulmairnicitaṃ sugandhibhirnikāmapuṣpairbakulaiśca sarvaśaḥ|
aśokapuṃnāgavanaiḥ supuṣpitairdvirephamālākulapuṣpasaṃcayaiḥ|| 30.24||
kvacit praphullāmbujareṇurūṣitairvihaṃgamaiścārukalapraṇādibhiḥ|
vināditaṃ sārasahaṃsanādibhiḥ pramattadātyūharutaiśca valgubhiḥ|| 30.25||
kvacicca cakrāhvarutopanāditaṃ kvacicca kādambakadambakāyutam|
kvacicca kāraṇḍavanādanāditaṃ kvacicca mattālikulākulīkṛtam|| 30.26||
madākulābhirbhramarāṅganābhirniṣevitaṃ cārusugandhipuṣpam|
kvacit supuṣpaiḥ sahakāravṛkṣairlatopagūḍhaistilakaiśca gūḍham|| 30.27||
pragītavidyādharasiddhacāraṇaṃ pranṛttanityānugatāpsarogaṇam|
prahṛṣṭanānāvidhapakṣisevitaṃ pramattahārītakulopanāditam|| 30.28||
mṛgendranādākulasannamānasaiḥ kvacit kvacidbaddhakadambakaṃ mṛgaiḥ|
praphullanānāvidhacārupaṅkajaiḥ sarastaḍāgairupaśobhitaṃ kvacit|| 30.29||
niviḍaniculanīlaṃ nīlakaṇṭhābhirāmaṃ
kvacicca dantikṣatacāruvīrut kvacillatāliṅgitacāruvṛkṣam|
kvacidvilāsālasagāminībhirniṣevitaṃ kiṃpuruṣāṅganābhiḥ|| 30.31||
pārāvatadhvaninikūjitacāruśṛṅgairabhraṃkaṣaiḥ sitamanoharacārurūpaiḥ|
ākīrṇapuṣpanikarapraviviktahāsairvibhrājitaṃ tridaśadevakulairanekaiḥ|| 30.32||
phullotpalāgarusahasravitānayuktaistoyāśayaiḥ samanuśobhitadevamārgam|
mārgāntarāgalitapuṣpavicitrabhakti sambaddhagulmaviṭapairvihagairupetam|| 30.33||
tuṅgāgrairnīlapuṣpastabakabharanataprāntaśākhairaśokair
haṃsānāṃ pakṣapātapracalitakamalasvacchavistīrṇatoyaṃ
sāraṅgaiḥ kvacidupasevitapradeśaṃ
saṃsṛṣṭaiḥ kvacidupaliptakīrṇapuṣpair
phullātimuktakalatāgṛhalīnasiddhaṃ
puṣpotkarānilavighūrṇitapādapāgram
candrāṃśujāladhavalaistilakairmanojñaiḥ
kvacidañjanacūrṇābhaiḥ kvacidvidrumasaṃnibhaiḥ|
kvacit kāñcanasaṃkāśaiḥ puṣpairācitabhūtalam|| 30.41||
puṃnāgeṣu dvijaśatavirutaṃ raktāśokastabakabharanatam|
ramyopāntaṃ klamaharapavanaṃ phullābjeṣu bhramaravilasitam|| 30.42||
sakalabhuvanabhartā lokanāthastadānīṃ
devyuvāca|
udyānaṃ darśitaṃ deva śobhayā parayā yutam|
kṣetrasya tu guṇān sarvān punarvaktum ihārhasi|| 30.44||
asya kṣetrasya māhātmyam avimuktasya tat tadā|
śrutvāpi na hi me tṛptirato bhūyo vadasva me|| 30.45||
deva uvāca|
idaṃ guhyatamaṃ kṣetraṃ sadā vārāṇasī mama|
sarveṣām eva jantūnāṃ heturmokṣasya sarvadā|| 30.46||
asmin siddhāḥ sadā devi madīyaṃ vratam āśritāḥ|
nānāliṅgadharā nityaṃ mama lokābhikāṅkṣiṇaḥ|
abhyasyanti paraṃ yogaṃ yuktātmāno jitendriyāḥ|| 30.47||
nānāvṛkṣasamākīrṇe nānāvihagasevite|
kamalotpalapuṣpāḍhyaiḥ sarobhiḥ samalaṃkṛte|| 30.48||
apsarogaṇagandharvaiḥ sadā saṃsevite śubhe|
rocate me sadāvāso yena kāryeṇa tacchṛṇu|| 30.49||
manmanā mama bhaktaśca mayi sarvārpitakriyaḥ|
yathā mokṣam ihāpnoti anyatra na tathā kvacit|| 30.50||
etanmama puraṃ divyaṃ guhyādguhyataraṃ mahat|
brahmādayo vijānanti ye ca siddhā mumukṣavaḥ|
ataḥ priyam idaṃ kṣetram asmācceha ratirmama|| 30.51||
vimuktaṃ na mayā yasmānmokṣyate vā kadācana|
mama kṣetram idaṃ tasmādavimuktam iti smṛtam|| 30.52||
naimiśe 'atha kurukṣetre gaṅgādvāre 'atha puṣkare|
snānāt saṃsevanādvāpi na mokṣaḥ prāpyate yataḥ|
iha samprāpyate yena tata etadviśiṣyate|| 30.53||
prayāge vā bhavenmokṣa iha vā matparigrahāt|
prayāgādapi tīrthāgryādidam eva mahat smṛtam|| 30.54||
jaigīṣavyaḥ parāṃ siddhiṃ yo gataḥ sa mahātapāḥ|
asya kṣetrasya māhātmyādbhaktyā ca mama bhāvataḥ|| 30.55||
jaigīṣavyaguhā śreṣṭhā yogināṃ sthānam iṣyate|
dhyāyatastatra māṃ nityaṃ yogāgnirdīpyate bhṛśam|
kaivalyaṃ paramaṃ yāti devānām api durlabham|| 30.56||
avyaktaliṅgairmunibhiḥ sarvasiddhāntavedibhiḥ|
iha samprāpyate mokṣo durlabho 'anyatra karhicit|| 30.57||
tebhyaścāhaṃ prayacchāmi yogaiśvaryam anuttamam|
ātmanaścaiva sāyujyam īpsitaṃ sthānam eva ca|| 30.58||
kuberaḥ sa mahāyakṣastathā sarvārpitakriyaḥ|
kṣetrasaṃsevanāddevi gaṇeśatvam avāpa ha|| 30.59||
saṃvarto bhavitā yaśca so 'api bhaktyā mamaiva tu|
ihaivārādhya māṃ devi siddhiṃ yāsyatyanuttamām|| 30.60||
parāśarasuto yogī ṛṣirvyāso mahātapāḥ|
dharmavaktā bhaviṣyaśca vedasaṃsthāpravartakaḥ|
raṃsyate so 'api padmākṣi kṣetre 'asmin munipuṃgavaḥ|| 30.61||
brahmā devarṣibhiḥ sārdhaṃ viṣṇurvāyurdivākaraḥ|
devarājastathā śakro ye 'api cānye divaukasaḥ|
upāsate mahātmānaḥ sarve mām iha suvrate|| 30.62||
anye ca yoginaḥ siddhāśchannarūpā mahāvrate|
ananyamanaso bhūtvā mām ihopāsate sadā|| 30.63||
alarkaśca purīm etāṃ matprasādādavāpsyati|
sa caināṃ pūrvavat kṛtvā caturvarṇasamākulām|| 30.64||
sphītāṃ janapadākīrṇāṃ bhuktvā ca suciraṃ nṛpaḥ|
mayi sarvārpitaprāṇo mām eva pratipatsyate|| 30.65||
tataḥ prabhṛti cārvaṅgi ye 'api kṣetranivāsinaḥ|
gṛhiṇo liṅgino vāpi madbhaktā matparāyaṇāḥ|
matprasādādgamiṣyanti mokṣaṃ paramadurgamam|| 30.66||
viṣayāsaktacitto 'api tyaktadharmaratirnaraḥ|
iha kṣetre mṛtaḥ so 'api saṃsāraṃ na punarviśet|| 30.67||
ye punarnirmamā dhīrāḥ sattvasthā vijitendriyāḥ|
vratinaśca nirārambhāḥ sarvato mayi bhāvitāḥ|| 30.68||
dehabhedaṃ samāsādya dhīmantaḥ saṅgavarjitāḥ|
gatā eva paraṃ mokṣaṃ prasādānmama suvrate|| 30.69||
janmāntarasahasreṣu yuñjan yogī yam āpnuyāt|
tam ihaiva paraṃ mokṣaṃ maraṇādadhigacchati|| 30.70||
etat saṃkṣepato devi kṣetrasyāsya mahat phalam|
avimuktasya kathitaṃ mayā te guhyam uttamam|| 30.71||
ataḥ parataraṃ nāsti kṣetraṃ guhyam itīśvari|
etadbudhyanti yogajñā ye ca yogīśvarā bhuvi|| 30.72||
etadeva paraṃ jñānam etadeva paraṃ śivam|
etadeva paraṃ brahma etadeva paraṃ padam|| 30.73||
vārāṇasīti bhuvanatrayasārabhūtā
etat smṛtaṃ priyatamaṃ mama devi nityaṃ
iti skandapurāṇe triṃśattamo .adhyāyaḥ||

triṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
udyānāni tato devaḥ sthānāni ca tathātmanaḥ|
ākhyāya himavatputryā vicacāra tadā punaḥ|| 30a.1||
so 'apaśyata tadā vipraṃ tapyamānaṃ paraṃ tapaḥ|
putraṃ śataśalākasya jaigīṣavyaṃ tapodhanam|| 30a.2||
sa liṅgaṃ devadevasya pratiṣṭhāpyārcayan sadā|
bhasmaśāyī bhasmadigdho nṛttagītairatoṣayat|| 30a.3||
japyena vṛṣanādaiśca tapasā bhāvitaḥ śuciḥ|
tam evaṃ vartamānaṃ tu bhaktyā paramayā yutam|| 30a.4||
bhagavān sahasābhyetya idaṃ vacanam abravīt|
jaigīṣavya mahābuddhe paśya māṃ divyacakṣuṣā|| 30a.5||
tuṣṭo 'asmi varadaścāsmi brūhi yat te manogatam|
sa evam ukto devena somaṃ dṛṣṭvā trilocanam|
praṇamya śirasā pādāvavadat parayā mudā|| 30a.6||
jaigīṣavya uvāca|
namaḥ sarvārthasiddhāya yogasiddhāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ pinākahastāya himavannilayāya ca|| 30a.7||
namaḥ pavanavegāya dhyeyāya dhyānibhiḥ sadā|
namaḥ somāya hemne ca hemamālādharāya ca|| 30a.8||
namo gaṇādhipataye namaḥ śāntendriyāya ca|
yogasāhāyyakartre ca sahasopaśamāya ca|| 30a.9||
namo mṛtyuharāyaiva namaḥ śokaharāya ca|
namaḥ siddhipradātre ca siddhasiddhipradāya ca|| 30a.10||
dhāriṇe sarvalokānāṃ sarvalokeśvarāya ca|
namo daśārdhavarṇāya saṃsārāpanudāya ca|| 30a.11||
namaḥ saṃsāraparāya apāraparamāya ca|
svayaṃ mantre ca manase durvijñeyāya vai namaḥ|| 30a.12||
namaḥ kālakalājñāya sakalāyākalāya ca||
namastattvādhivāsāya pretādhipataye namaḥ|| 30a.13||
namaḥ krodhavihīnāya krodhādhipataye namaḥ|
namaḥ śramāya śramiṇe śramāpanayanāya ca|| 30a.14||
namo jñānarasajñāya jñānine 'ajñānahāriṇe|
saktāya caiva tapasi aiśvaryaniratāya ca|| 30a.15||
namo jñānānubandhāya ajñānavinivartine|
namaḥ sarvānubhāvāya bhāvānugatacetase|| 30a.16||
namaḥ śamadamādhvāya mṛtyudūtāpahāriṇe|
namaḥ śailādināthāya śailādigaṇapāya ca|| 30a.17||
namo yogarahasyāya yogadāya namo namaḥ|
mahyaṃ sarvātmanā kāmān prayaccha bhagavan prabho|| 30a.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evaṃ stūyamānaśca bhaktyā paramayāpi ca|
tuṣṭastutoṣa bhūyo 'asya idaṃ cainam uvāca ha|| 30a.19||
devadeva uvāca|
ajaraścāmaraścaiva sarvaśokavivarjitaḥ|
mahāyogī mahāvīryo yogaiśvaryasamanvitaḥ|| 30a.20||
prabhāvāccāsya guhyasya kṣetrasya mama śāśvatam|
yoge 'aṣṭaguṇam aiśvaryaṃ prāpsyase paramaṃ mahat|| 30a.21||
bhaviṣyasi dvijaśreṣṭha yogācāryaśca viśrutaḥ|
yaścedaṃ tvatkṛtaṃ liṅgaṃ niyamenārcayiṣyati|| 30a.22||
yonayaḥ (?) sapta gatvā tu yogeśatvam avāpsyati|
jaigīṣavya guhāṃ cemāṃ prāpya yo yokṣyate dvijaḥ|| 30a.23||
saptarātraṃ sa yuktātmā sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
māsena pūrvāṃ jātiṃ ca pūrvādhītaṃ ca vetsyati|| 30a.24||
ekarātraṃ gatiṃ śuddhāṃ dvābhyāṃ tārayate pitR̥n|
trirātreṇa vyatītāṃśca parān sapta ca tārayet|
ato bhūyaśca kiṃ te 'adya jaigīṣavya dadānyaham|| 30a.25||
jaigīṣavya uvāca|
bhagavan devadeveśa iccheyaṃ me manogatā|
ato 'ahaṃ nānyadicchāmi yogākṣayyāt paraṃ hi tam|| 30a.26||
tvayi bhaktiśca nityaṃ syāt some sagaṇapeśvare|
anutsekaṃ tathā kṣāntiṃ śamaṃ damam athāpi ca|| 30a.27||
na cāpyabhibhavaṃ kuryānna ca tejovamānanām|
etān varānahaṃ deva sadecchāmi mahādyute|| 30a.28||
devadeva uvāca|
ete tava bhaviṣyanti ajayyatvaṃ ca yogibhiḥ|
icchato darśanaṃ caiva bhaviṣyati ca te mama|| 30a.29||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaḥ pārāśaryo mayā saha|
sanandī sagaṇaścaiva bhaktānugrahalipsayā|| 30a.30||
tapyato yakṣarājasya kṛtvā hṛdi maheśvaram|
varadānāya deveśo jagāma puratastadā|| 30a.31||
atha dṛṣṭvā tripādaṃ ca hrasvabāhūrupādakam|
tapyamānaṃ tapo ghoraṃ sutaṃ visravasastadā|| 30a.32||
dṛṣṭvovāca tato devaḥ kuberaṃ dīptatejasam|
tapasā bhāvitaṃ vyāsa tvagasthiparisaṃsthitam|| 30a.33||
devadeva uvāca|
bho bho visravasaḥ putra cakṣurdivyaṃ dadāmi te|
somaṃ paśya mahāsattva māṃ tvaṃ divyena cakṣuṣā|| 30a.34||
tataḥ sa dṛṣṭvā deveśaṃ sāmbaṃ nandipurassaram|
praṇamya karṣitaḥ samyagutthātuṃ na śaśāka ha|| 30a.35||
abalaṃ taṃ samālakṣya utthāne 'aśaktam īśvaraḥ|
uvācottiṣṭha bhadraṃ te balaṃ paurāṇam astu te|| 30a.36||
tata utthāya jānubhyāṃ kubero hyavatiṣṭhata|
pārśvagāṃ caiva netreṇa devīm ālokayan sthitaḥ|| 30a.37||
iyaṃ sā parvatasutā sarvalokanamaskṛtā|
mātā lokatrayasyāsya mahāyogabalānvitā|| 30a.38||
aho 'asyāstapaso vīryam aho dīptiraho balam|
yā prabhoḥ sarvalokasya patnītvaṃ prajagāma ha|| 30a.39||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tam evaṃbhūtamanasam īkṣamāṇaṃ ca pārvatīm|
bubodha devī buddhvā ca cukopa parameśvarī|| 30a.40||
sā kruddhvā tu kuberasya vāmam akṣi sudīptimat|
viśuṣkaṃ kakṣam ādīptā dadāhāgneḥ śikhā yathā|| 30a.41||
punaścāsya vināśāya kuberasya śubhānanā|
matiṃ dadhre tapoyonirathainām avadaddharaḥ|| 30a.42||
mā krudho devi yakṣasya bhaktasyāsya tapasvinaḥ|
yaśasvī dhārmikaścāyaṃ bhaktastvāṃ ca viśeṣataḥ|| 30a.43||
kautūhalatayā hyeṣa tvāṃ nirīkṣitavān śubhe|
prasādaṃ kuru bālasya dhanadasya maheśvari|| 30a.44||
devyuvāca|
eṣo 'asakṛnmāṃ deveśa vīkṣate 'avinayāt prabho|
minoti na guṇān deva kasmānmama puraḥ sthitaḥ|| 30a.45||
tejasāṃ yo 'aprameyānāṃ kuryānmohena laṅghanam|
so 'alpavīryo vinaśyeta pataṅgo 'agnim ivāgataḥ|| 30a.46||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tām evaṃ krodhatāmrākṣīṃ kruddhāṃ saṃprekṣya śaṃkarīm|
uvāca madhuraṃ ślakṣṇaṃ girīndratanayāṃ vacaḥ|| 30a.47||
bravīmi tvāṃ mahābhāge mā krudho jagato 'araṇi|
tvayā sṛṣṭaṃ jagat sarvaṃ prakṛtistvaṃ sureśvari|| 30a.48||
putraste 'ayaṃ yato devi tasmānna kroddhum arhasi|
mātaraṃ caiva putrasya vīkṣamāṇasya śobhane|| 30a.49||
na doṣo 'asti na caivāsya tvayi ceto vimohitam|
tasmāt tvam eva devyasya prapannasya natasya ca|
prasādaṃ kuru deveśa kuberasya yathepsitam|| 30a.50||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sā tathā devadevena proktā girivarātmajā|
prasādam akarot tasya prasannā cedam abravīt|| 30a.51||
devyuvāca|
kubera yat te duritaṃ kṣantaṃ tat te mayānagha|
tuṣṭāsmi mā kṛthāścaivaṃ punastejasvilaṅghanam|| 30a.52||
yat tvidaṃ te mayā dagdham īkṣamāṇasya locanam|
etat tathaiva bhavatu piṅgalaṃ dīptimacca ha|| 30a.53||
anena cāṅkito loke bhaviṣyasi na saṃśayaḥ|
ekākṣipiṅgalo nāmnā khyātaḥ sarvatra pūjitaḥ|| 30a.54||
caritaṃ yat tapaścedam akṣayaṃ tacca te 'avyayam|
saubhāgyam uttamaṃ caiva matprasādādbhaviṣyati|| 30a.55||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā tato devī virarāma śubhānanā|
bhagavān varado 'asmīti kuberam avadat tataḥ|| 30a.56||
athaivam ukto devena kubero hṛṣṭamānasaḥ|
tuṣṭāva devaṃ devīṃ ca śirasā prāñjalirnataḥ|| 30a.57||
kubera uvāca|
namaḥ paṭṭiśahastāya kirīṭavaradhāriṇe|
namo valayadhāriṇyai dhāriṇyai darpaṇasya ca|| 30a.58||
namaḥ sarvāṅgakeśāya dīrghakeśyai namo namaḥ|
namo mekhaladhāriṇyai namo mauñjīdharāya ca|| 30a.59||
namaścitraśikhaṇḍinyai namaḥ piṅgajaṭābhṛte|
namo jñānāya tanave bhūtādhipataye namaḥ|| 30a.60||
namastārābhidhāriṇyai siṃhoraskāya vai namaḥ|
namo ratnāgryadhāriṇyai namaścandrārdhamaulaye|| 30a.61||
namaḥ prakṛtaye caiva namo 'astu puruṣāya ca|
namo 'astu buddhaye caiva ahaṃkārāya vai namaḥ|| 30a.62||
namo 'astu rataye caiva sukhāya ca namo namaḥ|
namaḥ kṛtyai karmaṇe ca ārambhāya samāptaye|| 30a.63||
namo yajñāya mantrāya dakṣiṇāyai ṛce namaḥ|
namaḥ sāmne 'atha yajuṣe chandase ṣṭutaye namaḥ|| 30a.64||
namo 'agraye ca vedyai ca svāhāyai haviṣe namaḥ|
namo lakṣmyai śriye caiva namo dharmāya vedhase|| 30a.65||
icchāyai rataye caiva namaḥ sampadvirāgiṇe|
namaḥ siddhyai tathā puṣṭyai tuṣṭyai kṣāntyai namo namaḥ|| 30a.66||
namaḥ svadhāyai kavyāya havyāya ca namo namaḥ|
namo vedyāya vidyāyai namaḥ śarvāya bhaktaye|| 30a.67||
layāyotpattaye caiva sthityai saṃsāraṇāya ca|
mokṣāya muktaye caiva namaḥ kālāya mṛtyave|| 30a.68||
namaste bhagavan deva saha devyā jagatpate|
diśa no bhūtabhavyeśa yanme manasi saṃsthitam|| 30a.69||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ paṭhate nityaṃ stavaṃ prātaḥ samutthitaḥ|
japaṃśca vipro vaiśyo vā śūdraḥ kṣatriya eva vā|| 30a.70||
tasya tuṣṭo dhaneśastu prayacchati mahaddhanam|
somaśca bhagavāṃstuṣṭo gatim iṣṭāṃ prayacchati|| 30a.71||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ hi saṃstutastena kubereṇa jagatpatiḥ|
uvāca varado 'asmīti brūhi viśravasaḥ suta|| 30a.72||
kubera uvāca|
tvattaḥ prasādaṃ satataṃ bhaktiṃ ca tvayi śāśvatīm|
bhagavaṃstvāṃ ca paśyeyaṃ vara eṣo 'astu me vibho|| 30a.73||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam astviti tat sarvaṃ pradāya bhagavāñchivaḥ|
ātmanā saha sakhyaṃ ca dadau ātyantikaṃ tadā|| 30a.74||
devadeva uvāca|
gṛhāṇa caitāṃ śibikāṃ narayuktām asaṃginīm|
lokān yatheṣṭā/llokeśa yām āruhya cariṣyasi|| 30a.75||
imāṃ caivāśaniṃ divyām apratīghātalakṣaṇām|
gṛhāṇāyudham etat te bhaviṣyatyariduḥsaham|| 30a.76||
astraṃ ca te prayacchāmi tava nāmnā bhaviṣyati|
kauberam iti vikhyātaṃ mohanaṃ sarvadehinām|| 30a.77||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa devastuṣṭātmā mālāṃ svīyām aninditām|
ābabaddhāsya śirasi bhāskarākāravarcasam|| 30a.78||
kuśeśayānāṃ phullānāṃ sragdāma ca manoramam|
ābabaddhāsya kaṇṭhe vai prīyamāṇa umāpatiḥ|| 30a.79||
prakāmaṃ darśanaṃ cāsya dattvā caiva dhaneśatām|
jagāma bhagavān somastato 'anyaṃ deśam īpsitam|| 30a.80||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya idaṃ tu kuberasya varadānam aśeṣataḥ|
śṛṇuyācchrāvayedvāpi nityaṃ viprān samāhitaḥ|| 30a.81||
dhanavān rūpasampannaḥ putrapautrasamanvitaḥ|
kulajñānabalopeto jāyate sa mṛto naraḥ|| 30a.82||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha devī mahābhāgā sahitā śambhunā tadā|
saṃcintya pañcacūḍāstu tapantyo 'apsarasaḥ śubhāḥ|| 30a.83||
kṛśāṅgyo bhaktimatyaśca tapasā dagdhakilbiṣāḥ|
kāruṇyāhṛtacetaskā devaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 30a.84||
etāsāṃ tapyamānānāṃ yoṣitāṃ varam uttamam|
dadāmīpsitam īśāna tanme 'anujñātum arhasI|
tasyā vijñaptim ākarṇya bhagavānidam abravīt|| 30a.85||
devadeva uvāca|
evaṃ kuru mahābhāge bhaktānugraham īpsitam|
vaidikyo 'apsaraso hyetāḥ pañcacūḍā iti smṛtāḥ|| 30a.86||
tvāṃ kṛtvā hṛdi tapyante vara ābhyaḥ pradīyatām|
tataḥ sā devadevena tathā samanucoditā|
pañcacūḍāḥ samāgamya vaca etaduvāca ha|| 30a.87||
tuṣṭāsmyapsarasaḥ sākṣāt paśyadhvaṃ māṃ śucismitāḥ|
dadāmi vo varāniṣṭān ye vo hṛdayasaṃsthitāḥ|| 30a.88||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tā evam uktāḥ pārvatyā vaidikyo 'apsarasaḥ śubhāḥ|
devīṃ dṛṣṭvā praṇamyaināṃ śirasā pādayornatāḥ|| 30a.89||
aśrupūrṇekṣaṇā dīnāḥ saṃstabhyātmānam ātmanā|
śirasyañjalim ādhāya tuṣṭuvuḥ sahitāḥ samam|| 30a.90||
apsarasa ūcuḥ|
namaḥ siddhyai namastuṣṭyai kriyāyai buddhaye namaḥ
namaḥ kīrtyai namaḥ satyai ulka(a)jāyai tatheṣṭaye|| 30a.91||
namaḥ pṛthivyai kalyāṇyai śriyai lakṣmyai namo namaḥ|
namaḥ sudhāyai svāhāyai svadhāyai ditaye namaḥ|| 30a.92||
namo 'astu taḍite caiva saudāmanyai namo namaḥ|
sāvatryai cātha gāyatryai vedamātre namo namaḥ|| 30a.93||
namaḥ parvatakanyāyai mataye smṛtaye namaḥ|
namaḥ parvatavāsinyai rudrāṇyai ca namo namaḥ|| 30a.94||
namaḥ prakṛtaye caiva jyotsnāyai ṛddhaye namaḥ|
śobhāyai dīptaye caiva bhāskaragraharaśmaye|| 30a.95||
gatyāyai gataye caiva indrāṇyai muktaye namaḥ|
niyatyai sarite caiva gaṅgāyai sūtaye namaḥ|| 30a.96||
hetave prītaye caiva namaḥ karaṇavṛttaye|
namaḥ saṃtataye caiva irāyai vṛttaye namaḥ|| 30a.97||
vāruṇyai ca śaraṇyāyai śāntyai kāntyai namo namaḥ|
kauśikyai ca namaste 'astu kātyāyanyai namo namaḥ|| 30a.98||
namaḥ saṃnataye caiva mahimne ca namo namaḥ|
aṇimāyai namaste 'astu laghimāyai namo namaḥ|| 30a.99||
pūjayai te namaścaiva śitibāhve ca sṛptaye|
saṃjñāyai ca namaste 'astu gire 'atha smṛtaye namaḥ|| 30a.100||
namaste 'astu sarasvatyai jihvāyai dṛṣṭaye namaḥ|
namo mahiṣaghātinyai tathā śumbhaniśumbhayoḥ|| 30a.101||
namaḥ siṃharathinyai ca śūlinyai ca namo namaḥ|
namo mudgaradhāriṇyai kavacinyai namo namaḥ|| 30a.102||
namaḥ kuṇḍaladhāriṇyai dhāriṇyai jagato namaḥ|
namo dhanurdharāyai ca khaḍginyai ca namo namaḥ|| 30a.103||
namaḥ picchadhvajinyai ca dhāriṇyai paṭṭiśasya ca|
namo 'astu bhūtamātre ca skandamātre namo namaḥ|| 30a.104||
viśākhaśākhayormātre naigameśasya caiva hi|
jātyai sarvasurāṇāṃ ca devatāyai vanasya ca|| 30a.105||
āryāyai ca namo nityaṃ śikhaṇḍinyai namo namaḥ|
namo nīlaśikhaṇḍinyai dīrghaveṇyai namo namaḥ|| 30a.106||
namo 'astu tanumadhyāyai devatāyai dhanasya ca|
namo dhṛtyai namaścityai kīrtaye ca namo namaḥ|| 30a.107||
strīṇāṃ saubhāgyadāyinyai dhāriṇyai ca namo namaḥ|
rākānumataye caiva sinīvālyai namo namaḥ|| 30a.108||
namaḥ kriyāyai śraddhāyai medhāyai ca namo namaḥ|
namo 'astu dhāraṇāyai ca ūhāyai ca namo namaḥ|| 30a.109||
apohāyai namaste 'astu vaṣaṭprakṛtaye namaḥ|
namaḥ samādhaye caiva spṛhāyai cittaye namaḥ|| 30a.110||
vedanāyai namaste 'astu bṛhadukthyai namo namaḥ|
namaḥ prabhāyai śuddhāyai śuddhaye śucaye namaḥ|| 30a.111||
namastryambakabhāryāyai vidyāyai ca namo namaḥ|
dīkṣāyai dakṣiṇāyai ca jvālāyai ca namo namaḥ|| 30a.112||
indriyāṇāṃ pravṛttyai ca nivṛttyai caiva karmaṇām|
śrutaye sarvavedānāṃ bhavānyai ca namo namaḥ|| 30a.113||
durgāyai durgatāriṇyai dhāriṇyai sarvadehinām|
namaste sarvadevatye namaste lokabhāvini|| 30a.114||
namaḥ śāntyai namaḥ kāntyai namaḥ patnyai harasya ca|
namo 'astvadityai dānavyai vitānāyai namo namaḥ|| 30a.115||
namaḥ śivāyai kartryai ca prabhāvāyai namo namaḥ|
mṛkaṇḍvai mārdabāhvai ca tathā surabhaye namaḥ|| 30a.116||
vinatāyai tathā lakṣmyai surasāyai namo namaḥ|
namaste śitikaṇṭhinyai namaste sarvataḥ sadā|
diśa naḥ sumanāḥ sarvaṃ yat kiṃciddhṛdaye sthitam|| 30a.117||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya idaṃ paṭhate nityaṃ naraḥ strī vā samāhitaḥ|
sa rātriṣu kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ tyajet sarvam aśeṣataḥ|| 30a.118||
śayāno japate yaśca prayato vyāsa nityaśaḥ|
divākṛtaṃ sa jahyāt tu mṛtaśca sugatiṃ vrajet|| 30a.119||
yaścaitacchṛṇuyānnityaṃ dvijān vā śrāvayet sadā|
sa dehabhedam āsādya pañcacūḍapriyo bhavet|| 30a.120||
yaścedaṃ prajapan martyastyajet prāṇān sudustyajān|
vimāne sūryasaṃkāśe apsarogaṇasevite|| 30a.121||
sarvapāpavinirmukto ramedvarṣāyutaṃ śatam|
yaśca bhaktyā paramayā tithau niyamavān naraḥ|| 30a.122||
devī[ma]bhyarcya japate sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
japanādeva tapasā dehe bhinne ca bhaktimān|
sa bhūtvānucaro devyāḥ puṇye loke mahīyate|| 30a.123||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tābhirevaṃ stutā devī sthitā devasya saṃnidhau|
uvāca hṛṣyamāṇāsyā pañcacūḍā idaṃ vacaḥ|| 30a.124||
śṛṇutāpsarasaḥ sarvāstapaso 'asya mahat phalam|
yaccāpi parayā bhaktyā māṃ prapannāḥ stha śobhanāḥ|| 30a.125||
ajarāśca viśokāśca nityaṃ muditamānasāḥ|
priyāśca sarvalokasya bhaviṣyatha mamājñayā|| 30a.126||
brūta yaccāpi kiṃcidvo hṛdi sthitam aśaṅkitāḥ|
sarvaṃ dāsyāmi tadvo 'ahaṃ mā cirāyata durvyathāḥ|| 30a.127||
pañcacūḍā ūcuḥ|
devi puṃsāṃ striyaḥ sarvāḥ kāryārthaṃ viditaṃ ca te|
arthinaste ca nastāvat yāvat kāryaṃ samāpyate|
samāpte caiva te kārye parā iva bhavanti naḥ|| 30a.128||
taddevi yadi tuṣṭāsi yadi deyo varaśca naḥ|
sarvastrīṇāṃ mahādevi bhavantu puruṣā vaśāḥ|| 30a.129||
devyuvāca|
adyaprabhṛti lokeṣu sarvastrīṇāṃ narāḥ sadā|
vaśyā bhavantu sarvatra sarvakāryakarāśca ha|| 30a.130||
[ā]dau paścācca sarvābhyo hiraṇyaṃ paśavaḥ striyaḥ|
sarvabhogāṃśca dāsyantu vaśagāḥ sarvathāpi ca|| 30a.131||
vyalīkānyapi kurvantyo bahūni vividhāni ca|
priyā eva bhaviṣyanti pāpaṃ na ca bhavet sadā|| 30a.132||
mātaraṃ pitaraṃ bhrātR̥n suhṛdo 'atha sutānapi|
akāryāṇi kariṣyanti strīṇāṃ vaśyatvam āgatāḥ|| 30a.133||
paśyanto 'api vyalīkāni doṣān vaikṛtyam eva ca|
naiva dravanti te puṃsāṃ madvarānmohitendriyāḥ|| 30a.134||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sā devadevasya patnī himavataḥ sutā|
mālyadāma gṛhītvā tu bhrāmayantī śubhānanā|| 30a.135||
bhava nārya iti prāha hasantī priyam avyayā|
bhrāmyamāṇasya dāmno 'asya yānyaśīryanta bhūtale|| 30a.136||
kusumānyabhavaṃstāni nāryaḥ kamalalocanāḥ|
tā uvāca purā yūyaṃ jarākṣayavivarjitāḥ|| 30a.137||
jaganmohakarāḥ sarvāḥ puṃsāṃ hṛdayabandhanāḥ|
dṛṣṭisparśavilāseṣu āviśya jagatītrayam|| 30a.138||
-- -- -- -- -- puruṣān strīvaśāṃśca kariṣyatha|
narāḥ sarve ca yuṣmāsu bhaviṣyanti sadā ratāḥ|| 30a.139||
vṛttiḥ śubhā bhavitrī ca sarvāsāṃ mama tejasā|
puṃsāṃ strībhogasiddhyarthaṃ strīṇāṃ ratyartham eva ca|| 30a.140||
kriyāḥ śubhāṅgasaṃskārā divyā ye mānuṣāśca ha|
bahurūpāśca tā bhūtvā viviśuḥ sarvadāṅganāḥ|| 30a.141||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ devī tadā vyāsa sṛṣṭvā tā vai visṛjya ca|
uvācāpsaraso brūta kiṃ vo bhūyaḥ karomyaham|| 30a.142||
tāstuṣṭamanasaścāpi ūcurvyāsa bhavema hi|
devānāṃ mānuṣāṇāṃ ca avaśyāścaiva rakṣasām|
tā uvāca tato devī evaṃ loke bhaviṣyatha|| 30a.143||
tataḥ sa sahito devyā sanandī parameśvaraḥ|
gaṇaiḥ sarvaiśca sahito gṛhān svān āviśat prabhuḥ|| 30a.144||
bhaganayananipātī daityadarpāpahārī surakamalahimaughaḥ kāmayajñāgnihantā|
jaladavṛṣabhayāyī sarvaduḥkhāntakārī samaravṛṣabhaketuścandramaulirjagāma|| 30a.145||
iti skandapurāṇe vārāṇasyavalokane
jaigīṣavyadhanadapañcadūḍānāṃ varapradānanāmā
triṃśo .adhyāyaḥ||

triṃśoo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan piṅgalaḥ kena gaṇatvaṃ samupāgataḥ|
annadatvaṃ ca samprāpto vārāṇasyāṃ mahādyutiḥ|| 30b.1||
kṣetrapālaḥ kathaṃ jātaḥ priyatvaṃ ca kathaṃ gataḥ|
etadicchāmi kathitaṃ śrotuṃ brahmasuta tvayā|| 30b.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vyāsa yathā lebhe gaṇeśatvaṃ sa piṅgalaḥ|
annadatvaṃ ca lokānāṃ sthānaṃ vārāṇasīṃ ca hi|| 30b.3||
pūrṇabhadrasutaḥ śrīmān āsīdyakṣaḥ pratāpavān|
harikeśa iti khyāto brahmaṇyo dhārmikaśca ha|| 30b.4||
tasya janmaprabhṛtyeva bhave bhaktiranuttamā|
tadāśīstannamaskārastanniṣṭhastatparāyaṇaḥ|| 30b.5||
āsīnaśca śayānaśca gacchaṃstiṣṭhannanuvrajan|
bhuñjāno 'atha piban vāpi rudram evānvacintayat|| 30b.6||
tam evaṃ yuktamanasaṃ pūrṇabhadraḥ pitābravīt|
na tvā putam ahaṃ manye durjāto yastvam anyathā|| 30b.7||
na hi yakṣakulīnānām etadvṛttaṃ bhavatyuta|
guhyakā vata yūyaṃ vai svabhāvāt krūracetasaḥ|| 30b.8||
kravyādāścaiva kiṃbhakṣā hiṃsāśīlāśca putraka|
maivaṃ kārṣīrna no vṛttirevaṃ dṛṣṭā mahātmanām|
svayambhuvā yathā sṛṣṭā saiva vṛttiḥ praśasyate|| 30b.9||
harikeśa uvāca|
sṛṣṭā caivāpraśastā ca garhitā sādhubhiḥ sadā|
vṛttiḥ svayambhuvihitā tyaktavyā yadi no bhavet|| 30b.10||
āśramāntarajaṃ karma na kuryurgṛhiṇastataḥ|
hitvā manuṣyabhāvaṃ ca karmabhirvividhaiśca ha|| 30b.11||
devatvaṃ no vimārgeyurmānuṣyaṃ jātim eva ca|
atha cedvihitaṃ teṣāṃ karma tatprāptisaṃsṛtam|
mamāpi vihitaṃ paśya karma tannātra saṃśayaḥ|| 30b.12||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktaḥ putreṇa pūrṇabhadraḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca niṣkrama kṣipraṃ gaccha tvaṃ yatra rocate|| 30b.13||
tataḥ sa nirgatastyaktvā gṛhasaṃbandhibāndhavān|
vārāṇasī samāsādya tapastepe suduścaram|| 30b.14||
sthāṇubhūto hyanimiṣaḥ śuṣkakāṣṭhopalopamaḥ|
saṃniyamyendriyagrāmam avātiṣṭhata niścalaḥ|| 30b.15||
atha tasyaivam aniśaṃ tatparasya tadāśiṣaḥ|
sahasram ekaṃ varṣāṇāṃ divyam atyativartata|| 30b.16||
valmīkena samākrānto bhakṣyamāṇaḥ pipīlikaiḥ|
vajrasūcīmukhairvyāsa vidhyamānastathaiva ca|| 30b.17||
nirmāṃsarudhiratvagvai kundaśaṅkhendusaprabhaḥ|
asthiśeṣo 'abhavat sarvo devaścaivam amanyata|| 30b.18||
etasminnantare devī vyajñāpayata śaṃkaram|
udyānaṃ punarevedaṃ draṣṭum icchāmi sarvada|| 30b.19||
kṣetrasya caiva māhātmyaṃ śrotuṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me|
yataśca priyam etat te yaccāsya phalam uttamam|| 30b.20||
iti vijñāpito devaḥ pārvatyā bhuvaneśvaraḥ|
sarvaṃ pṛṣṭaṃ yathānyāyam ākhyātum upacakrame|| 30b.21||
nirjagāma ca deveśaḥ pārvatyā saha śaṃkaraḥ|
udyānaṃ darśayāmāsa devyā devaḥ pinākadhṛk|| 30b.22||
praphullanānāvidhagulmaśobhitaṃ latāpratānāvanataṃ manoramam|
virūḍhapuṣpaiḥ paritaḥ priyaṅgubhiḥ supuṣpitaiḥ kaṇṭakitaiśca ketakaiḥ|| 30b.23||
tamālagulmairnicitaṃ sugandhibhirnikāmapuṣpairbakulaiśca sarvaśaḥ|
aśokapuṃnāgavanaiḥ supuṣpitairdvirephamālākulapuṣpasaṃcayaiḥ|| 30b.24||
kvacit praphullāmbujareṇurūṣitairvihaṃgamaiścārukalapraṇādibhiḥ|
vināditaṃ sārasahaṃsamadgubhiḥ pramattadātyūharutaiśca valgubhiḥ|| 30b.25||
kvacicca cakrāhvarutopanāditaṃ kvacicca kādambakadambakairyutam|
kvacicca kāraṇḍavanādanāditaṃ kvacicca mattālikulākulīkṛtam|| 30b.26||
madākulābhirbhramarāṅganābhirniṣevitaṃ cārusugandhipuṣpam|
kvacit supuṣpaiḥ sahakāravṛkṣairlatopagūḍhaistilakaiśca gūḍham|| 30b.27||
pragītavidyādharasiddhacāraṇaṃ pranṛttanityānugatāpsarogaṇam|
prahṛṣṭanānāvidhapakṣisevitaṃ pramattahārītakulopanāditam|| 30b.28||
mṛgendranādākulasannamānasaiḥ kvacit kvacidbaddhakadambakaṃ mṛgaiḥ|
praphullanānāvidhacārupaṅkajaiḥ sarastaḍāgairupaśobhitaṃ kvacit|| 30b.29||
niviḍaniculalīnānīlakaṇṭhābhirāmaṃ
madamuditavihaṃgavrātanādābhirāmam|
kusumitataruśākhālīnamattadvirephaṃ
navakiśalayaśobhāśobhitaprāntaśākham|| 30b.30||
kvacicca dantikṣatacāruvīrut kvacillatāliṅgitacāruvṛkṣam|
kvacidvilāsālasagāminībhirniṣevitaṃ kiṃpuruṣāṅganābhiḥ|| 30b.31||
pārāvatadhvanivikūjitacāruśṛṅgairabhraṃkaṣaiḥ sitamanoharacārurūpaiḥ|
ākīrṇapuṣpanikarapraviviktahāsairvibhrājitaṃ tridaśadevakulairanekaiḥ|| 30b.32||
phullotpalāmbujasahasravitānayuktaistoyāśayaiḥ samanuśobhitadevamārgam|
mārgāntarāgalitapuṣpavicitrabhaktaiḥ sambaddhagulmaviṭapairvihagairupetam|| 30b.33||
tuṅgāgrairnīlapuṣpastabakabharanataprāntaśākhairaśokair
mattālivrātagītaśrutisukhajananairbhāsitaṃ tanmanojñaiḥ|
rātrau candraprabhāsā ku[su]mitatilakairekatāṃ samprayātaṃ
chāyāsuptaprabuddhasthitahariṇakulāluptadarbhāṅkurāgram|| 30b.34||
haṃsānāṃ pakṣavātapracalitakamalasvacchavistīrṇatoyaṃ
toyānāṃ tīrajātapravikacakadalīvāṭanṛttanmayūram|
māyūraiḥ pakṣacandraiḥ kvacidapi patitai rañjitakṣmāpradeśaṃ
deśe deśe nilīnapramuditavilasanmattahārītavṛndam|| 30b.35||
sāraṅgaiḥ kvacidupasevitapradeśaṃ
saṃchannaṃ kusumacayaiḥ kvacidvicitraiḥ|
hṛṣṭābhiḥ kvacidapi kiṃnarāṅganābhiḥ
kṣībābhiḥ sumadhuragītavṛkṣaṣaṇḍam|| 30b.36||
saṃsṛṣṭaiḥ kvacidupari prakīrṇapuṣpair
āvāsaiḥ parivṛtapādapaṃ munīnām|
āmūlāt phalanicitaiḥ kvacidviśālair
uttuṅgaiḥ panasamahīruhairupetam|| 30b.37||
phullātimuktakalatāgṛhalīnasiddhaṃ
siddhāṅganākanakanūpurarāvaramyam|
ramyapriyaṅgutarumañjarisaktabhṛṅgaṃ
bhṛṅgāvalīśabalitāmrakadambapuṣpam|| 30b.38||
puṣpotkarānilavighūrṇitapādāpagram
agre surebhavinipāṭitavaṃśagulmam|
gulmāntaraprasṛtabhītamṛgīsamūham
ūhāvatāṃ tanubhṛtām apavaregadātṛ|| 30b.39||
candrāṃśujāladhavalaistilakairmanojñaiḥ
sindūrakuṅkumakusumbhanibhairaśokaiḥ|
cāmīkarapratisamairatha karṇikāraiḥ
puṣpotkarairupacitaṃ suviśālaśākhaiḥ|| 30b.40||
kvacidañjanacūrṇābhaiḥ kvacidvidrumasaṃnibhaiḥ|
kvacit kāñcanasaṃkāśaiḥ puṣpairācitabhūtalam|| 30b.41||
puṃnāgeṣu dvijaśatavirutaṃ raktāśokastabakabharanatam|
ramyopāntaṃ klamaharapavanaṃ phullābjeṣu bhramaravilasitam|| 30b.42||
sakalabhuvanabhartā lokanāthastadānīṃ
tuhinaśikhariputryā sārdham iṣṭairgaṇeśaiḥ|
vividhataruviśālaṃ mattahṛṣṭānyapuṣṭam
upavanam atiramyaṃ darśayāmāsa devyāḥ|| 30b.43||
devyuvāca|
udyānaṃ darśitaṃ deva śobhayā parayā yutam|
kṣetrasya tu gaṇān sarvān punarvaktum ihārhasi|| 30b.44||
asya kṣetrasya [mā]hātmyam avimuktasya tat tadā|
śrutvā hi na hi me tṛptirato bhūyo vadasva me|| 30b.45||
devadeva uvāca|
idaṃ guhyatamaṃ kṣetraṃ sadā vārāṇasī mama|
sarveṣām eva jantūnāṃ heturmokṣasya sarvadā|| 30b.46||
asmin siddhāḥ sadā devi madīyaṃ vratam āsthitāḥ|
nānāliṅgadharā nityaṃ mama lokābhikāṅkṣiṇaḥ|| 30b.47||
abhyasyanti paraṃ yogaṃ yuktātmāno jitendriyāḥ|
nānāvṛkṣalatākīrṇe nānāvihagasevite|| 30b.48||
kamalotpalapuṣpāḍhyaiḥ sarobhiḥ samalaṃkrṭe|
apsarogaṇagandharvaiḥ sadā saṃsevite śubhe|| 30b.49||
rocate me ihāvāso yena kāryeṇa tacchṛṇu|
manmanā mama bhaktaśca mayi sarvārpitakriyaḥ|| 30b.50||
yathā mokṣam ihāpnoti anyatra na tathā kvacit|
japadhyānodyatānāṃ ca jñāneṣu āraktacetasām|| 30b.51||
tamomohahatānāṃ ca vārāṇasyāṃ gatirnṛṇām|
atrotkramaṇakāle tu svayam eva maheśvaraḥ|| 30b.52||
dadāti tārakaṃ brahma yenāsau tanmayo bhavet|
evaṃ mama puraṃ divyaṃ guhyādguhyataraṃ mahat|| 30b.53||
brahmādayo vijānanti ye ca siddhā mumukṣavaḥ|
ataḥ priyam idaṃ kṣetraṃ yasmācceha ratirmama|| 30b.54||
vimuktaṃ na mayā yasmānmokṣyate vā kadā ca na|
mama kṣetram idaṃ tasmādavimuktam idaṃ smṛtam|| 30b.55||
naimiśe 'atha kurukṣetre gaṅgādvāre 'atha puṣkare|
snānāt saṃsevanāccāpi na mokṣaḥ prāpyate yataḥ|| 30b.56||
iha samprāpyate yena tata etadviśiṣyate|
prayāge vā bhavenmokṣa iha vā matparigrahāt|| 30b.57||
prayāgādapi tīrthāgryādidam eva mahat smṛtam|
jaigīṣavyaḥ parāṃ siddhiṃ yo gataḥ sa mahātapāḥ|| 30b.58||
asya kṣetrasya māhātmyādbhaktyā ca mama bhāvataḥ|
jaigīṣavyaguhā preṣṭhā yogināṃ sthānam iṣyate|| 30b.59||
dhyāyatastatra māṃ nityaṃ yogāgnirdīpyate bhṛśam|
kaivalyaṃ paramaṃ yāti devānām api durlabham|| 30b.60||
atra siddhiṃ parāṃ prāpto mārkaṇḍeyo mahātapāḥ|
bālakhilyāstathā siddhā asmin kṣetre sudurlabhe|| 30b.61||
ātreyā bhārgavāḥ siddhā asmin kṣetre sudurlabhe|
avyaktaliṅgairmunibhiḥ sarvasiddhāntavedibhiḥ|| 30b.62||
iha samprāpyate mokṣo durlabho 'anyatra karhicit|
tebhyaścāhaṃ prayacchāmi yogaiśvaryam anuttamam|| 30b.63||
ātmanaścaiva sāyujyam īpsitaṃ sthānam eva ca|
kuberaḥ sa mahāsattvastathā sarvārpitakriyaḥ|| 30b.64||
kṣetrasaṃsevanādeva dhaneśatvam avāpa ha|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 30b.65||
ihaivārādhya māṃ devi siddhiṃ yāsyatyanuttamām|
parāśarasuto yogī ṛṣirvyāso mahātapāḥ|| 30b.66||
mama bhakto bhaviṣyaśca vedasaṃsthāpravartakaḥ|
ramate so 'api padmākṣi kṣetre 'asmin munipuṃgavaḥ|| 30b.67||
brahmāpi ṛṣibhiḥ sārdhaṃ viṣṇurvāyurdivākaraḥ|
devarājastathā śakraḥ api cānye divaukasaḥ|| 30b.68||
upāsate mahātmānaḥ sarveśam iha suvrate|
ananyamanaso bhūtvā mām evopāsate sadā|| 30b.69||
ālarkaśca purīm etāṃ matprasādādavāpsyati|
sa caināṃ pūrvavat kṛtvā catuvarṇasamākulām|| 30b.70||
sphītāṃ janapadākīrṇāṃ bhuktvā ca suciraṃ tadā|
mayi sarvārpitaprāṇo mām eva pratipatsyate|| 30b.71||
tataḥ prabhṛti cārvāṅgi ye 'api kṣetranivāsinaḥ|
gṛhiṇo liṅgino vāpi madbhaktā matparāyaṇāḥ|| 30b.72||
matprasādādgamiṣyanti mokṣaṃ paramadurgamam|
viṣayāsaktacitto 'api tyaktadharmaratirnaraḥ|| 30b.73||
iha kṣetre mṛtaścāpi saṃsāraṃ na punarviśet|
ye punarnirmamā dhīrāḥ siddhāḥ syurvijitendriyāḥ|| 30b.74||
vratinaḥ sthānirāvasthāḥ (?) sarvato mayi bhāvitāḥ|
dehabhedaṃ samāsādya dhīmantaḥ sargavarjitāḥ|| 30b.75||
prapatsyante paraṃ mokṣaṃ prasanne mayi suvrate|
janmāntarasahasreṣu yuñjan yogam avāpnuyāt|
tadihaiva paraṃ mokṣaṃ maraṇādadhigacchati|| 30b.76||
brahmaghnagoghnagurutalpagacauravṛttir
na mo pa haṃ (?) -- -- -- -- niyatasvavṛttiḥ|
saṃsārabhūtadṛḍhapāśavimuktaśoko
vārāṇasīṃ mama purīṃ samupaiti lokaḥ|| 30b.77||
etat saṃkṣepato devi kṣetrasyāsya mahat phalam|
avimuktasya kathitaṃ mayā te guhyam uttamam|| 30b.78||
ataḥ parataraṃ nāsti siddhaṃ guhyam adhīśvari|
etadbudhyanti yogajñā ye ca yogaparā bhuvi|| 30b.79||
etadeva paraṃ jñānam etadeva paraṃ śivam|
etadeva paraṃ brahma etadeva paraṃ padam|| 30b.80||
vārāṇasī tu bhuvanatrayasārabhūtā
ramyā purī mama sadā girirājaputri|
yatrāgatā vividhaduṣkṛtakāriṇo 'api
pāpakṣayādvirajasaḥ śruti (?) yānti muktim|| 30b.81||
ya āgacchet kathaṃcicca purīṃ vārāṇasīṃ naraḥ|
tam upāyaṃ prakurvīta nirgacchenna punaryathā|| 30b.82||
yadīcchet saphalaṃ janma ko 'anyaṃ vedyāphalaṃ (?) tathā|
kāśīpuryāṃ tyajeddehaṃ yadīcchet paramaṃ padam|| 30b.83||
etat smṛtaṃ priyataṃ mama devi viśvaṃ (?)
kṣetraṃ vicitratarugulmanikāmapuṣpam|
asmin mṛtāstanubhṛtaḥ padam āpnuvanti
mokṣākhyam evaśivatāpi (?) na saṃśayo 'atra|| 30b.84||
iti skandapurāṇe vārāṇasīmāhātmyaṃ nāma triṃśattamo .adhyāyaḥ||

dvātriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
etasminneva kāle tu vyāsa dakṣaḥ prajāpatiḥ|
ayajat so 'aśvamedhena rājā prācetasātmajaḥ|| 32.1||
tatra devanikāyānāṃ bhāgadheyāni sarvaśaḥ|
havyavāhastadā tatrāvahanmantraiḥ samīritaḥ|| 32.2||
vahantaṃ tam apaśyacca devī girivarātmajā|
anusmarantī tadvairaṃ śāpakāraṇam eva ca|| 32.3||
uvāca cainaṃ girijā bodhayantī purātanam|
śliṣṭaṃ madhurayā vācā kāraṇena samanvitam|| 32.4||
tvaṃ devaḥ sarvadevānāṃ gatiśca śaraṇaṃ tathā|
tvayā vinā kathaṃ yajño vartate sarvadevapa|| 32.5||
devānāṃ bhāgadheyāni vahatyagnirayaṃ bhava|
nāyaṃ tava maheśāna kiṃ kāraṇam atidyute|| 32.6||
na sāmnā sidhyate karayaṃ vikrameṇa vinā prabho|
ayaṃ mūḍho 'avaliptaśca rājā prācetasātmajaḥ|| 32.7||
anusmaran pūrvavairaṃ naiva dāsyatyaśāsitaḥ|
dadhīcasya varaścāpi tvayā dattastadā prabho|
tasyāyam āgataḥ kālastadarthena vidhīyatām|| 32.8||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktastadā vyāsa bhagavān vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|
uvāca prahasan devīṃ pitā tava śucismite|| 32.9||
pūrvajanmani suśroṇi prajāpatisutaḥ śubhe|
mama tvaṃ bhāvavijñānaṃ kurvatī devi bhāṣase|| 32.10||
na hi duḥkhaṃ piturloke kascidicchati bhāmini|
evam uktā tadā vyāsa devena vimalātmanā|| 32.11||
lalāṭe bhṛkuṭīṃ kṛtvā tato devī āyatekṣaṇā|
krodhāt kareṇa nāsāgraṃ saṃmamarda śucismitā|| 32.12||
tasyāṃ saṃmṛdyamānāyāṃ nāsikāyām atiprabhā|
jajñe strī bhṛkuṭīvaktrā caturdaṃṣṭrā trilocanā|
baddhagodhāṃgulitrā ca kvacābaddhamekhalā| 13||
sakhaṅgā sadhanuṣkā ca satūṇīrā patākinī|
svādaśāsyā daśabhujā tanumadhyā tamonibhā|| 32.14||
ghanastanī pṛthukaṭī nāganāsoruravyayā|
bhadrakālīti tāṃ prāha devīṃ devī śubhānanā|| 32.15||
tato 'abravīt tadā devam eṣā sṛṣṭā mayā prabho|
tvam apyanyaṃ sṛja gaṇam anurūpaṃ namo 'astu me|| 32.16||
tato devastadā skandhaṃ svam avaikṣata bhāsvaram|
tasmājjajñe pumān divyastrailokyaṃ pradahanniva|| 32.17||
bhṛkuṭībhūṣitāsyaśca baddhagodhāṃgulitravān|
kavacī baddhatūṇīraḥ śarī khaṅgī śarāsanī|| 32.18||
tryakṣaścaturbhujaścaiva vajrasaṃhanano yuvā|
sa sṛṣṭaḥ praṇato bhūtvā harirnāmnā gaṇeśvaraḥ|| 32.19||
uvāca prāñjalirbhūtvā devadevaṃ sahomayā|
ājñāpaya sureśāna yat kartavyaṃ mayā vibho|| 32.20||
tataḥ sa bhagavānaha hariṃ taṃ gaṇanāyakam|
prācetasasutasyāsya yajñaṃ gaccha vināśaya|| 32.21||
bhadrakālyā sahāśu tvam etat kṛtyaṃ gaṇeśvara|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devo gaṇeśān kāmarūpiṇaḥ|| 32.22||
svagātrebhyo 'asṛjaddhīmān nānārūpadharān gaṇān|
pasparśa bāhuṃ samyak ca tasmājjātā mahābalāḥ|| 32.23||
koṭyastā navatiścaiva śataṃ caiva tadā prabhoḥ|
sa tāṃścovāca bhagavān yajñaṃ pramathatānaghāḥ|| 32.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastau tena sainyena mahatābhisamāvṛtau|
jagmatuḥ sāgaronnādameghāśanininādataiḥ|| 32.25||
devo 'api saha pārvatyā raibhyāśramasamīpataḥ|
sthitvāpaśyadgaṇeśānāṃ karma tadyajñanāśanam|| 32.26||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vṛkṣāḥ kanakhaleyāstu gaṅgādvārasamīpagāḥ|
suvarṇaśṛṅgaśca girirmeruparvatasannibhaḥ|| 32.27||
tasmin pradeśe dakṣasya yajño 'asāvabhavat tadā|
gaṇeśvarabalaṃ cāgādbhīmaṃ kālīpurogamam|| 32.28||
taṃ saṃprāpya mahābhāgāḥ sarve dīptānalaprabhāḥ|
ūcustaṃ yajamānaṃ ca ṛtvijo 'atha munīn surān|| 32.29||
vayaṃ hyanucarāḥ sarve śarvasya paramātmanaḥ|
ihābhilipsavaḥ prāptā bhāgān yacchadhvam īpsitān|| 32.30||
tapasā yajñabhāgārhā balena niyamena vā|
aiśvaryeṇātha yogena yena tena puro hi vaḥ|| 32.31||
sarvaṃ cāsmāsvapi hi tadvayam apyaṃśabhāginaḥ|
atha cet svāmino devāstena bhāgārhatāṃ gatāḥ|| 32.32||
svāmitve ca balaṃ hetustapo vā nātra saṃśayaḥ|
asmāsvevobhayaṃ tacca svāmitvaṃ tena no varam|| 32.33||
atha cet kasyacidiyam ājñā munisurottamāḥ|
bhāgo bhavadbhyo deyastu nāsmabhyam iti kathyatām|| 32.34||
taṃ brūta yo jñāpayati vetsyāmo hi vayaṃ tataḥ|
evam uktāstu hariṇā sarve devapuraḥsarāḥ|| 32.35||
ūcurmantrāḥ pramāṇaṃ vo bhāgaṃ prati gaṇeśvarāḥ|
mantrāpi ūcuḥ surān yūyaṃ tamopahatacetasaḥ|| 32.36||
yena prathamabhāgārthaṃ nāyajadhvaṃ maheśvaram|
mantraiste procyamānāpi naiva bhāgān daduryadā|| 32.37||
tadā yātāstato mantrā brahmalokaṃ sanātanam|
tataḥ śakrādayo devāḥ sarve ūcurgaṇeśvarān|| 32.38||
tyaktvā (?) -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- ---|
yuṣmān nihanmo vikramya sarvānevāgatān yudhi|| 32.39||
teṣāṃ sagarvaṃ tadvākyaṃ śrutvā hariramitrajit|
uvāca prahasan sarvānidaṃ vacanasūrjitam|| 32.40||
mantrāḥ pramāṇaṃ na kṛtā yuṣmābhirbalagarvitaiḥ|
yasmāt prasahya tasmādvo nāśayāmyadya garjitān|| 32.41||
ṛtvigbhirbhāgadheyaiśca saha yajñena codyataḥ|
yeṣāṃ ca lavattā vastān sarvān nāśayāmyaham|| 32.42||
evam uktvā sa tejasvī haribhadraḥ pratāpavān|
bhadrakālī ca saṃkruddhā abhidudravatuḥ surān|| 32.43||
gaṇeśvarāśca saṃkruddhā yūpānutpāṭya cikṣipuḥ|
prasthātrā saha hotāram aśvaṃ caiva gaṇeśvarāḥ|| 32.44||
gṛhītvā kupitāḥ sarve gaṅgāsrotasi cikṣipuḥ|
yajamānaṃ ca pāśena baddhvā ninyuryathāsukham|| 32.45||
vedīm anye kuśānanye sruco 'anye camasān pare|
vyanāśayaṃścikṣipuśca śālāścānye 'abhyadīpayan|| 32.46||
haribhadro 'api dīptātmā śakrasyodyacchataḥ karam|
vyaṣṭaṃbhayadadīnātmā tathānyeṣāṃ divaukasām|| 32.47||
bhagasya netre pūṣṇaśca daśanān ruṣitānanaḥ|
dhanuṣkoṭyā samāhatya miṣatāṃ saṃnyapātayat|| 32.48||
viṣṇoścakraṃ ca tadghoraṃ yugāntādityavarcasam|
vyaṣṭambhayadadīnātmā karasthaṃ na cacāla ha|| 32.49||
tuṣitāṃśca tathā devānudyuktān yuddhalālasān|
vāyavyāstreṇa saṃhatya pṛthivyāṃ tān nyapātayat|| 32.50||
anyāṃśca devān devo 'asau sarvān yuddhāya saṃsthitān|
mohanenāstravaryeṇa saṃmohayadaninditaḥ|| 32.51||
rājānaścāpi ye kecit tatrāyātā didṛkṣavaḥ|
tān sarvānastravīryeṇa svagṛhānanayadbalāt|| 32.52||
tat pravidhvastakalaśaṃ bhagnayūpasatoraṇam|
pradīpitamahāśālaṃ dṛṣṭvā yajño 'abhidudruve|| 32.53||
taṃ tadā mṛgarūpeṇa dhāvantaṃ gaganaṃ prati|
hariḥ śaraṃ sa sandhāya viśiraskam athākarot|| 32.54||
śaraṃ cāparam ādāya vīrabhadraḥ pratāpavān|
palāyamānaṃ taṃ yajñaṃ sasāra mṛgarūpiṇam|
nakṣatrasamatāṃ yātuṃ dvābaddhaṃ vītamabhyagāt|| 32.55||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ te nikṛtā vyāsa gaṇaiḥ kāltyā tathaiva ca|
hariṇā caiva devena sarve śaraṇam āgatās|| 32.56||
tān prapannāṃstadā sarvān devān samunilokapān|
hariḥ kālyā sahaivāha gacchadhvaṃ somam avyayam|
prasadhayadhvaṃ deveśaṃ tato vo bhavitā śamaḥ|| 32.57||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā hariṇā jagmurdevaṃ pramanyavaḥ|
prasādayitum avyagrā duḥkhaśokasamanvitāḥ|| 32.58||
tataste nātidūre tu sāmbaṃ sagaṇam īśvaram|
apaśyanta mahātmānaḥ sarve tadgatamānasāḥ|| 32.59||
te taṃ dṛṣṭvā praṇamyoccaistuṣṭuvurdīptatejasam|
vāgbhirāhavanīyābhiḥ kṛtvā brahmāṇam agrataḥ|| 32.60||
devā ūcuḥ|
namaste suraśatrughna surayajñapramardaka|
mahāyajña mahāsatva mahākratuśatastuta|| 32.61||
namo yajñavināśāya vedasarvasvadāya ca|
śipiviṣṭakṛte viṣṇornarasiṃhābhighātine|| 32.62||
mandarādrinivāsāya śubhasarvasvadāya ca|
mahāvimānayānāya ṛtuvighnakarāya ca|| 32.63||
mantrāntaḥ karaṇayaiva mantravratakarāya ca|
pūṣṇo dantavināśāya bhagnanetraharāya ca|| 32.64||
viṣṭambhanāya śakrasya viṣṇoścakrasya caiva hi|
namo yajñapraṇetre ca yajñotpattikarāya ca|| 32.65||
varadānādhigamyāya brahmaṇo janakāya ca|
vyāghracarmabhṛte tubhyaṃ kṛṣṇacarmāmbarāya ca|| 32.66||
namaḥ sragvaramālāya narapitre tathaiva ca|
utpādakāya viṣṇośca jayāya vijayāya ca|| 32.67||
namo manyuvināśāya vīrabhadraprajāya ca|
namo harṣāya kopāya gaṇeśvarasṛje namaḥ|| 32.68||
namo devānutāpāya mṛgabāṇārpaṇāya ca|
namaste bhagavan deva namaste bhagavañchiva|| 32.69||
namaste sarvalokeśa namaste lokabhāvana|
tvayā sṛṣṭam idaṃ viśvaṃ yajño devāśca yajñahan|
prasīda mā krudho 'asmākaṃ mā naḥ kṛtvā vināśaya|| 32.70||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ paṭhate nityaṃ prayataḥ prātarutthitaḥ|
na tasya vighnarūpāṇi kadācit saṃbhavantyuta|| 32.71||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto deveśastadā tān stuvataḥ sthitān|
uvāca prahasan vākyaṃ sarvātmā sarvabhāvanaḥ|| 32.72||
devadeva uvāca|
nāhaṃ kruddho bhavanto me nityam evātivallabhāḥ|
kruddhe hi mayi yuṣmākaṃ na syājjīvaṃ kṣaṇāntare|| 32.73||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā tadā devaḥ surāṇāṃ hitakāmyayā|
prāveśayat surān sarvāṃstatastān yogamāyayā|| 32.74||
sve śarīre mahādevo vismāpayitum ojasā|
te praviṣṭāstadā deham īśvarasya mahātmanaḥ|| 32.75||
saptalokasamāyuktam apaśyañjagad adbhutam|
te paribhramya tā/llokān kṛtsnān sarve bhayānvitāḥ|| 32.76||
pañcākṣaṃ gaṇapaṃ vīraṃ tatrāpaśyan samāgatāḥ|
tena te suraśārdūlāḥ sarve hi ūrdhvam atandritāḥ|| 32.77||
ākṣiptāstanmuhūrtena lokam anyam upāgatāḥ|
apaśyaṃste mahābhāgā nagaraṃ sūryasannibham|| 32.78||
sphāṭikenātimahatā prākāreṇābhisaṃvṛtam|
śṛṅgaiśca vividhiścitrairmaṇihemojjvalaiḥ śubhaiḥ|| 32.79||
tato 'aparam apaśyaṃste tanmadhye surasattamāḥ|
saptayojanakoṭīkaṃ samantānnagaraṃ śubham|| 32.80||
rājatenāvṛtaṃ divyaṃ prākāreṇenduvarcasā|
tasya madhye 'aparaṃ cordhvaṃ ṣaṭkoṭyā vistṛtaṃ puram|| 32.81||
jāmbūnadamayenaiva prākāreṇa susaṃvṛtam|
tasya madhye tataścānyat pañcakoṭīpramāṇataḥ|| 32.82||
indranīlopalenaiva prākāreṇa samāvṛtam|
tasya madhye hyapaśyaṃste vibudhā munisattama|| 32.83||
caturyojanakoṭīkaṃ vistārāyāmataḥ samam|
vaidūryopalayuktena prākāreṇābhisaṃvṛtam|| 32.84||
nagaraṃ tasya madhye ca trikoṭīyojanaṃ śubham|
sarvaratnavicitreṇa prākāreṇābhisaṃvṛtam|| 32.85||
teṣāṃ madhye janapadāḥ sarvaduḥkhavivarjitāḥ|
śuklābhijanasampannāḥ sarve ca sthirayauvanāḥ|| 32.86||
kṣutpisāvinirmuktā rogaśokavivarjitāḥ|
amarā jarayā tyaktā nityaṃ muditamānasāḥ|| 32.87||
dīrghikābhirvicitrābhirvāpībhiścāpyalaṃkṛtāḥ|
vṛkṣairnānāvidhaiścitraiḥ sadā puṣpaphalopagaiḥ|| 32.88||
sarvabhakṣān prasūyante vṛkṣāstatrāpare śubhāḥ|
apare cāpyalaṃkārān sarvavāsāṃsi cāpare|| 32.89||
apare sarvapuṣpāṇi sarvaṇyeva phalāni ca|
sarvabhāvāṃstathā cānye madhu cāmākṣikaṃ śubham|| 32.90||
apare kṣīriṇastatra vṛkṣā vyāsa mahāprabhāḥ|
kṣīraṃ kṣaranti te nityaṃ sarve gavyaṃ samanvitāḥ|| 32.91||
sarvā maṇimayī bhūmiḥ śubhā kāñcanavālukā|
udbhidānyudakānyatra giriprasravaṇāni ca|| 32.92||
na teṣu krodho lobho vā yuddhaṃ dveṣo 'atha matsaraḥ|
na moho naiva ca stambho na doṣāstatra cāpare|| 32.93||
tasya madhye puraṃ cānyaddvikoṭīvistṛtaṃ śubham|
padmarāgamayenaiva prākāreṇa pariṣkṛtam|| 32.94||
īdṛśāni purāṇi sma vyatikramya surāstataḥ|
koṭīyojanavistīrṇaṃ samantādvahnināvṛtam|| 32.95||
saṃvartakānalākāraṃ durnirīkṣyaṃ puraṃ mahat|
advāraṃ dadṛśurdivyam anantaṃ te surottamāḥ|| 32.96||
dṛṣṭvā jagmuḥ puraṃ caiva vismayaṃ bhayam eva ca|
tān bhītavadanān vyāsa vepamānān sureśvarān|
pañcākṣo gaṇapaḥ prāha mā bhīrbhavatu vaḥ surāḥ| 97||
idaṃ tat sumahadghoraṃ puraṃ ghorānalāvṛtam|
draṣṭvyaṃ vo mahātmano yatkṛte cāgatāstviha|| 32.98||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā sa pañcākṣaḥ śūlenānalavarcasā|
paśyatāṃ surasaṃghānāṃ dvāraṃ cakre mahābalaḥ|| 32.99||
te praviṣṭā mahātmānaḥ pañcākṣasahitāḥ surāḥ|
divyaṃ dadṛśire pūrṇaṃ siṃhānāṃ tat puraṃ mahat|| 32.100||
merumandarakalpānāṃ nakhadaṃṣṭrāvatāṃ tathā|
ghorāṇām agnivarṇānāṃ kruddhānām atitejasām|| 32.101||
teṣām ekastadā siṃhaśchittvā bandhanam ūrjitaḥ|
anvadhāvata saṃkruddhaḥ pralambitamahāsaṭaḥ|| 32.102||
tasya siṃhasya nādena bhairaveṇa divaukasaḥ|
viṣaṇṇavadanāḥ sarve pañcākṣaṃ śaraṇaṃ yayuḥ|| 32.103||
pañcākṣa uvāca|
na bhetavyaṃ surā devaṃ darśayāmyadhunā hi vaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ityuktā dadṛśuḥ śarvaṃ sahasā te sahomayā|
na caiva tat puraṃ vyāsa na siṃhaṃ nāpi kiṃcana|| 32.104||
vepamānā bhayeneśaṃ śaraṇaṃ paryupāgatāḥ|
tāñcharaṇyaḥ sa bhagavānuvāca prahasaṃstadā|| 32.105||
āmantrya sarvān deveśo bhayatrastān divaukasaḥ|
dṛṣṭā hi vo mama krodhāḥ siṃharūpā bhayānakāḥ|| 32.106||
ekena teṣāṃ raudreṇa yūyaṃ sarve 'api tarjitāḥ|
yadi sarvānahaṃ krodhādvisṛjeyaṃ kadācana|| 32.107||
na bhaveta na sandehaḥ sarve yūyaṃ kṣaṇāntare|
iyaṃ tu devī yuṣmākaṃ kupitā parvatātmajā|
etāṃ prasādayata vai nāhaṃ kupyāmi vaḥ surāḥ|| 32.108||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktavati svāminyuddhatātāmralocanā|
devī devīṃ mukhādghorāṃ sasṛje bhayavardhanīm|| 32.109||
daṃṣṭrākarālavadanāṃ bahupādakarāṅgulim|
dhanuḥparaśukhaḍgogracakraśūleṣudhāriṇīm|| 32.110||
jvalardakasahasrāṃśutejasaṃ viśvarūpiṇīm|
daśayojanasāhasrastasyā dehaḥ pramāṇataḥ|| 32.111||
tayābhibhūtāste devā vadhyamānāśca sarvaśaḥ|
na śekuḥ purataḥ sthātuṃ vyāghrānmṛgagaṇā iva|| 32.112||
tato vyathitacittāste kālakarṇībhayāt surāḥ|
bhasmarāśiṃ sthitaṃ pārśve devasya viviśurbhayāt|| 32.113||
tān dṛṣṭvā bhasmakūṭaṃ tu praviṣṭāñcharaṇārthinaḥ|
surān bhasmaviliptāṅgān devī devīṃ nyaṣedhayat|| 32.114||
devyuvāca|
kālakarṇi nivartasva mā vadhīḥ surasattamān|
ete pāśupatībhūtā bhasmanā digdhamūrtayaḥ|| 32.115||
etat paśupatiproktaṃ vrataṃ pāśupataṃ purā|
yadbhasmanā pavitreṇa snānaṃ snānebhya uttamam|| 32.116||
ete bhagavato vaśyam anugrāhyāḥ surottamāḥ|
bhasma yena praviṣṭāstu tasmānmaitān vināśaya|| 32.117||
raudrāḥ paśava ete hi praveśādbhasmaso 'adhunā|
jātāśca gaṇapāḥ sarve hantavyā na tvayeśvari|| 32.118||
naiṣāṃ mṛtyuḥ prabhavati śaṅkarārpitacetasām|
mayā hyetadvrataṃ śarvaṃ caritaṃ sārvakāmikam|| 32.119||
ityuktā kālakarṇī tu devyā bhairavarūpiṇī|
nyavartata surebhyastu kopaṃ tatyāja cotthitam|| 32.120||
kālakarṇīṃ nivṛttāṃ tu dṛṣṭvā te 'api surāstataḥ|
śāntaṃ ca bhayam atyugraṃ tuṣṭuvurhimavatsutām|| 32.121||
devā ūcuḥ|
haravaramahiṣīṃ mahādevapatnīṃ priyāṃ tryambakasyāmbikāṃ
vācam ekākṣarāṃ lokasaṃhārakartrīmumāṃ devadevasya
pātnīṃ śubhāṃ śaṃkhakundenduhārāmbugaurogradaṃṣṭrāṃ
jayām āhaverdurnirīkṣyām acintyogradṛṣṭiṃ viśālekṣaṇāṃ
pītakośeyavastrāṃ mahāśūlaghaṇṭāpatākādhvajāṃ divyagandhājyadhūpapriyāṃ
kāladaṇḍāsicarmograhastāṃ vapāśoṇitāntravasāpūrṇabhāṇḍāṃ
diśāṃ dakṣiṇāṃ cārucāmīkarābaddhapaṭṭāṃ
yugāntānalābhekṣaṇām aṭṭahāsān sṛjantīṃ
yathākāmakartrīm anaṅgāyudhāvikṣatāṃ śūrasenāṃ nadīṃ viśrutāṃ
mandarāvāsanityāṃ diviṣṭhāṃ prapadyāmahe
kānasī(ṣṭi)m
asuramahiṣadaraṇīṃ dāraṇīṃ sundubheḥ sundamārīṃ niśumbhasya
mṛtyuṃ vibhāṃ somamūryāgnibhāsāṃ sṛjatkāntim iṣṭapradāṃ
śokaduḥkhārtihartrīṃ viśekām aghorāṃ ghanām antakasyāntakartrīṃ
munerjāmadagnyasya corjjāṃ tathā
rājarājñīṃ manojñāṃ karālāṃ kṣapāṃ daṇḍanītiṃ sthitisiddhim
iṣṭāṃ śubhāṃ kālarātrīm
aparṇāṃ samādhiṃ śaraṇyāṃ nagendrādhivāsapriyāṃ kṣīrodanityāṃ śubhām
mahākiṃkiṇīkāṃ prakīrṇordhvakeśīṃ pradīptāgnisandhyābhrarāgatviṣam
baddhagodhāṅgulitrāṃ trinetrāṃ jaṭākeśaraktāmbujābaddhamālāṃ viśalyām
anaṅgārinetrolkajāṃ hemamālānibaddhasrajāṃ dīrghaveṇīṃ suveṇīm
yaśaḥkīrtiyuktāṃ mayūrāṅgajābaddhacitradhvajāṃ rājasāṃ śāntikartrīm
prapadye 'aham ekāṃ sadā
bhujaṅgaśatakṛtāṅgadāṃ mahādānavaprāṇaśauṇḍām
citābhasmarūkṣāṅgakeśīṃ mahājānulambodarāṃ sarpayajñopavītarddhavaktroddhṛtākṣārdhapādārdrahastāvataṃsām
mahāmekhalādāmalambadvicitrasrajāṃ mahāmeghatūryogravāditranṛttapriyām
gītahāsyapralāpapramodapriyāṃ jāpyahomopavāsādavāsāpravāsādhivāsātiriktām
mahāyogavijñātasārānusārograsārāṃ dhṛtim
jyānughaṇṭāvabaddhograśabdāṃ mahāmeghavajraprapātodadhiprakyatīvrograghoṣām
kriyāṃ dīkṣitānāṃ ca
dīkṣāṃ virūpākṣabhāryāṃ harasyārdhadehādhivāsāṃ prapadye mukholykodbhavāṃ devīm
ādyāṃ parāṃ pārvatīṃ sarvavidyādhidevīṃ gatiṃ yamaniyamadamātmabhūtām
pitR̥ṇāṃ ca kanyāṃ śubhāṃ parvatendrātmajāṃ dakṣayajñāntakartrīm
bhavasyārdhadehāśritādityadantāvapātāṃ surendrāgrahastapratistambhanīm
viṣṇukeśāpahartrīṃ mahāsiṃhayuktātivāhāṃ mahābhairavāṃ bhīṣitām
skandacandrāraṇīṃ mātaraṃ hastivaktrasya cāgryāṃ viśākhasya
janmāraṇīṃ nandino naigameṣasya cotpādanīṃ sarvalokasya
cādyāraṇīṃ pūjyāṃ mātaraṃ yogināṃ yoginīṃ dhyāyamānāṃ dhṛtim
devaviprairmahāyogatarkairagamyāṃ viśiṣṭeṣṭaśiṣṭādhivāsāṃ ca
lakṣmīṃ narī(?)bhūrbhuvaḥsvarjanassatyavairājamāhātmyalokāraṇīm
kāraṇīm indriyāṇām ahaṅkāratanmātrakartrīṃ tamassatvarāgapravṛttim
parāṃ ca pravṛttiṃ maheśasya śaktiṃ tathā cetanāṃ sarvavijñanacintyām
prapadyāma devīm umāṃ mātaraṃ diśa
tvaṃ sukhaṃ mātarasmāsu tuṣṭā
mahādevapatnīṃ śubhāṃ yāṃ vayaṃ cintyām aikayā saṃvidā dhyāyamānāḥ sadā
dāruṇaṃ cāpi sarvaṃ kṛtaṃ yat tvayā (?) tacca no jātikoṭīsahasreṣu
pūrvaṃ kṛtaṃ yat kariṣyāma yat kurma tat sarvam evaṃ ca dadyāśca
naḥ sarvam arthaṃ sakāmaṃ tathārogyam ūrjāṃ śriyaṃ jñānavijñānanedhāstathā
dhāraṇāṃ tarkam ūhām apohaṃ dhṛtiṃ cārthabhāvaṃ gatiṃ caiva divyāṃ tathā
dharmanityatvam etāṃśca ye cāpyato 'anye guṇāstāṃśca
sarvāñjuṣasvādya devi tubhyaṃ namaḥ|| 123--144||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sā saṃstutā devī devairhṛṣṭena cetasā|
tryambakānugrahāccaiva devāṃstuṣṭābravīdidam|| 32.145||
devyuvāca|
gacchadhvaṃ vijvarāḥ sarve tuṣṭāhaṃ vo na saṃśayaḥ|
maivaṃ kārṣṭa punardevā mā vināśo hi vo bhavet|| 32.146||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa devaḥ prahasan kapardī nīlalohitaḥ|
prakṛtisthān surān sarvāṃścakāra suraśatruhā|| 32.147||
uvāca caitān deveśo gacchadhvaṃ vigatajvarāḥ|
yajñaścaiva yadā kṛtyaṃ tadāyaṃ bhavitā hi vaḥ|| 32.148||
saśirasko diteḥ putrā mantreṇānena sandhitaḥ|
tataḥ stotraṃ ca mantraṃ ca sandhānakaram avyayam|
dadau ātharvaṇaṃ devaḥ provācedaṃ ca susvaram|| 32.149||
devadeva uvāca|
nakṣatrasamatāṃ yātu yajño 'ayaṃ surasattamāḥ|
sṛgānusārī devo 'api hairasya bhavatvayam|| 32.150||
bhadrakālī hariścaiva gaṇāśceme mahābalāḥ|
sarve bhadrā bhaviṣyanti yuṣmākam amarāḥ sadā|| 32.151||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktā bhagavatā devāste brahmāṇā saha|
śirobhiḥ praṇatāḥ sarve śarvam ūcuridaṃ vacaḥ|| 32.152||
eṣa tāvat kratuśreṣṭhastavaiva bhavatu prabho|
sarvaḥ surapate deva śatam abhyarcyate 'avyaya|| 32.153||
bhāgānāṃ sarvayajñeṣu tubhyaṃ sarvaṃ dadāmahe|
evam ukto 'atha deveśaḥ suraiḥ sarvaiḥ sureśvaraḥ|| 32.154||
cakāra rūpaṃ paramaṃ sarvadevamayaṃ śubham|
svātmānaṃ te tadā devā hyapaśyanta maheśvare|| 32.155||
śirobāhūrupādeṣu vastihastodarādiṣu|
avasthitān mahātmāno munīṃścaiva tapodhanān|| 32.156||
sa tadrūpaṃ tadā kṛtvā devān provāca śaṃkaraḥ|
sarve yūyaṃ mahātmāno maccharīrasamudbhavāḥ|| 32.157||
yuṣmākaṃ ca śarīrāṇi manmayāni prapaśyata|
tataste devatā vyāsa sarvaṃ rudrātmakaṃ jagat|| 32.158||
ātmānaṃ cāpyapaśyanta vismayāpannacetasaḥ|
evaṃ sa teṣāṃ deveśo darśayitvātmano balam|| 32.159||
uvāca suraśārdūlān dṛṣṭā hyetā vibhūtayaḥ|
yo yāṃ pūjayate mūrtiṃ bhaktyā paramayā yutaḥ|| 32.160||
tasya tāṃ mūrtim āsthāya pūjāṃ gṛhṇāmyahaṃ surāḥ|
na bhāgadheyaiḥ kṛtyaṃ me bhāgadheyāni vaḥ surāḥ|
sarvāṇyeva dadāmyadya yāta sarve gatajvarāḥ|| 32.161||
devā ūcuḥ|
ghuyam etat paraṃ deva tvayāsmākaṃ nidarśitam|
evaṃ yo vetsyate martyaḥ sa lokān prāpsyate 'avyayān|| 32.162||
idaṃ ca bhagavan sthānaṃ bhadreśvaram iti śrutam|
bhaviṣyati jagacchreṣṭhaṃ puṇyebhyaḥ puṇyavattamam|| 32.163||
samantādyojanaṃ caiva rudrakṣetraṃ sanātanam|
mṛgo 'atra gaṇapo deva vallabhaste bhaviṣyati|| 32.164||
yaścedaṃ kīrtayennityaṃ kalya utthāya yajñahan|
śrāvayeccāpi viprebhyaḥ sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 32.165||
bhadrakarṇahrade cāsmin snātvā yo 'abhyarcayeddharam|
sādhayitvā caruṃ caiva bhojayedbrāhmaṇāñchuciḥ|| 32.166||
sa sarvapāpanirmukto yatra tatra mṛto naraḥ|
modate 'apsarasāṃ madhye divi deva ivāparaḥ|| 32.167||
yatra coktaṃ tvayā deva sthitena bhagavan prabho|
harabhadreti puṇyo 'ayaṃ tvatprasādādbhavatvajaḥ|| 32.168||
aśvamedhasya yat puṇyaṃ samyagiṣṭasya yajñahan|
tadatra deva bhavatu narasyābhyarcataḥ sadā|| 32.169||
parityakṣyati yaścātra kaścit prāṇān narottamaḥ|
haribhadrasya sa gaṇo bhaviṣyati mahābalaḥ|| 32.170||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam astviti sa procya mandaraṃ cārukandaram|
jagāma bhagavāñcharvaḥ somo gaṇaśatirvṛtaḥ|| 32.171||
devāpi rājñā sahitāstasmiṃsthāne yathāsukham|
tasthurbrahmā ca viṣṇuśca jagmaturdevapṛṣṭhataḥ|| 32.172||
sa gatvā stokam adhvānam ubhābhyāṃ sahitaḥ prabhuḥ|
nātidūre tataḥ prāha tiṣṭha viṣṇo mahābala|| 32.173||
sa praṇamya tataḥ pādau harasya puruṣottamaḥ|
tasthau āmraṃ samālambya sa kubjaḥ samapadyata|| 32.174||
yasmādāmraṃ samālambya tasmin deśe sthito hariḥ|
nirīkṣamāṇo deveśaṃ deśastasmādabhūdasau|| 32.175||
kubjāmraka iti khyāto viṣṇoḥ kṣetraṃ samṛddhimat|
puṇyaṃ nivartanādviṣṇorgosahasraphalapradam|| 32.176||
nātidūraṃ tato gatvā bhūvo devaḥ pitāmaham|
nivartetyabravīdvyāsa gaganaṃ ca samāviśat|| 32.177||
tasmin viyadgate deve brahmā prāñjalirunmukhaḥ|
pradakṣiṇaṃ samāvṛtya praṇamya prayayau tataḥ|| 32.178||
yasmāt tatra haraṃ tena kurvatā vai pradakṣiṇam|
āvarttaḥ svaśarīrasya prakṛtaḥ puṇyakarmaṇā|| 32.179||
tasmāt sa deśo vikhyāto brahmāvartteti śobhanaḥ|
aśvamedhaphalaṃ tatra snātaḥ prāpnoti mānavaḥ|| 32.180||
sādhayitvā caruṃ cātra bhojayitvā tathā dvijān|
prāṇān parityajya tato brahmalokamavāpnuyāt|| 32.181||
tato 'abhyetya suraiḥ sārrdhaṃ brahmā viṣṇupuraḥsaraiḥ|
bhadreśvare paśupatermahimānam athākarot|| 32.182||
sa liṅgaṃ tatra saṃsthāpya pūjāṃ kṛtvātibhāsvaraṃ |
bhadrakarṇahrade snātvā saha devairdivaṃ yayau|| 32.183||
taṃ prayāntaṃ tadā dakṣo brahmāṇam idam ūcivān|
kartavyaṃ kiṃ mayā deva mama tadbrūhi pṛcchataḥ|| 32.184||
pitāmaha uvāca|
prasādaya maheṣvāsaṃ śarvam ugraṃ kapardinam|
tato yajñasamāptiṃ ca lokāṃśca prāpsyase 'avyayān|| 32.185||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto devena brahmaṇā vyāsa tattvataḥ|
liṅgaṃ kanakhale kṛtvā rudram abhyarcayat tadā|| 32.186||
tasya saṃvatsaraśate pūrṇe divye prajāpateḥ|
mahādevo 'adrijāṃ prāha prahasan girimūrdhani|| 32.187||
prācetasātmajo devi sthitastapasi saṃyataḥ|
paśyainaṃ madgateneśe cetasā samavasthitam|| 32.188||
tato dṛṣṭvā mahādevī vāyubhakṣam avasthitam|
liṅge paramayā bhaktyā pūjayantaṃ maheśvaram|| 32.189||
uvāca hṛṣitā devī devaṃ sarvasurārcitam|
kṛtāñjalipuṭā vyāsa sarvadevapatiṃ patim|| 32.190||
devyuvāca|
kṣudro 'ayaṃ duṣṭacetāśca stabdho mānī ca durmatiḥ|
diṣṭyā tvayā vinikṛtastvām eva śaraṇaṃ gataḥ|| 32.191||
tadasya duṣṭabhāvasya prapannasya maheśvara|
kṣantum arhasi bhaktasya tvām asyārthe prasādaye|| 32.192||
devadeva uvāca|
tvam eva devi yacchāsmai varāniṣṭān yathāsukham|
anujñātā mayā subhru tvam evāsya varaṃ diśa|| 32.193||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastau devadeveśau saṅgatau svagaṇairvṛtau|
ūcatuḥ paśya dakṣāvāṃ tuṣṭau divyena cakṣuṣā|| 32.194||
prācetasa mahābhāga varadau svo mahātapas|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 32.195||
śāpaśāntyartham et te varaṃ dadmi tavepsitam|
yaste yajño gaṇairdhvastaḥ phalaṃ tasya tvam āpnuhi|| 32.196||
kāmarūpadharaḥ śrīmān gaṇeśaśca bhavasva me|
akṣayaścāmaraścaiva duḥkhaśokavivarjitaḥ|
bhaviṣyasi mahābhāga mama caiva samīpagaḥ|| 32.197||
devyuvāca|
śṛṇuṣva bhūyaḥ kiṃ cānyat prayacchatu maheśvaraḥ|
suduṣkaram api hyeṣa varaṃ dadyāt tvayārthitaḥ|| 32.198||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktastadā dakṣo himavatsutayā tayā|
prāñjaliḥ praṇato bhūtvā idam āha mahāmatiḥ|| 32.199||
dakṣa uvāca|
yo devastribhuvanajanmanāśakartā yaṃ mūḍhā na viduranuktam ekam eva|
bhaktānām aśubhaharaṃ pinākapāṇiṃ taṃ devaṃ śaraṇagatā vayaṃ sabhāryam|| 32.200||
yo 'ajñānādasuratayātimānamohānnāsmābhiḥ saha khalu pūjito 'adriputryā|
yaḥ śāpaṃ mama ruṣito dadau sureśastaṃ devaṃ śaraṇagatā vayaṃ sabhāryam|| 32.201||
yaḥ sraṣṭā suragaṇayakṣarākṣasānāṃ siddhānāṃ ditisutadānavendranR̥ṇām|
bhūtānāṃ paśumṛgapakṣipattagānāṃ taṃ devaṃ śaraṇagatā vayaṃ sabhāryam|| 32.202||
yaḥ kodhānmahadasṛjadgaṇeśvareśaṃ siṃhendraṃ harim amitaprabhāvarūpam|
patnīṃ cāpyabhitaguṇaprabhāvayuktāṃ taṃ devaṃ śaraṇagatā vayaṃ sabhāryam|| 32.203||
yo devān sahavaruṇān savittagopān sabrahmān saśatamakhān saviṣṇuvāyūn|
indrāgryān samunimahāyudhān vijigye taṃ devaṃ śaraṇagatā vayaṃ sabhāryam|| 32.204||
yat kiṃcit tvayi kaluṣaṃ kṛtaṃ ca duṣṭaṃ hyajñānādapi ca hi rāgadoṣamohāt|
tat sarvaṃ mama saha bhāryayādya śarvo viśvātmā kṣamatu mahānubhāvabhāvāt|| 32.205||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tata evaṃ sa deveśaṃ stutvā sāsrāvilekṣaṇaḥ|
prasārya bāhū sarveṇa śarīreṇāpatadbhuvi|| 32.206||
taṃ prapannaṃ tadā devo dakṣaṃ sāsrāvilekṣaṇam|
devyā saha mahabhāga svayam utthāpayadbalī|| 32.207||
tasyāśrūṇyapatan bhūmau bindubhūtāni tatra vai|
tāni saṃhatya viprendra nadī tu samapadyata|| 32.208||
tām uvāca tato devo nadīṃ vai puṇyalakṣaṇām|
arjunādaśrubindostvaṃ yasmāddevi viniḥsṛtā|| 32.209||
tasmāt khyātā bhavitrī tvam arjunā nāmataḥ śubhā|
parva parva samāsādya vahiṣyasi mahāyaśe|| 32.210||
aśvamedhaphalaṃ cāpi tvayi snāto hyavāpsyati|
mṛtaśca tava tīre 'asmin niyamenetareṇa vā|| 32.211||
na punarjanma mānuṣye durgatiṃ copalapsyate|
trirātropoṣito yaśca caruṃ kṛtvā nivedya ca|| 32.212||
brāhmaṇaṃ bhojayet snātastvayi so 'api gamiṣyati|
gavāṃ lokaṃ mahātejā na ca tasmāt patiṣyati|| 32.213||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa sṛṣṭvā saritaṃ kṛtvā caivāpyanugraham|
tam āśvāsya sureśastu dakṣaṃ prāha nṛpaṃ tadā|| 32.214||
devadeva uvāca|
gataṃ tasmādbhayaṃ te 'astu gaṇeśo me bhava priyaḥ|
brūhi kiṃ te punaḥ sādho dadāni varam īpsitam|| 32.215||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha dakṣastadovāca praṇamya śubhayā girā|
bhūya bhūyaḥ samāśvasya nirīkṣya ca punaḥ punaḥ|| 32.216||
dakṣa uvāca|
yadi tuṣṭo 'asi me deva bhavatvetat tavāvyaya|
sthānaṃ pavitraṃ puṇyaṃ ca vara eṣo 'astu me śiva|| 32.217||
devadeva uvāca|
ete ca munikanye dve tapa āsthāya duṣkaram|
karṇaiḥ saṃvatsare pūrṇe khalena ca yato 'aśanam|| 32.218||
kṛtavatyau mahābhāge tvaṃ ca dakṣo yataḥ sthitaḥ|
idaṃ kanakhalaṃ tasmānmama sthānaṃ bhaviṣyati|| 32.219||
tīrthaṃ caiva mahat puṇyaṃ gaṅgāsāgarasannibham|
nātra pāpā na ca śaḥtā nāstikā na ca māninaḥ|| 32.220||
lapsyante vai sadā gantuṃ na ca vastuṃ kathaṃcana|
mṛto 'atra na punarjanma lapsyate mama tejasā|| 32.221||
atrābhigamya snātvā ca caruṃ kṛtvā tathaiva ca|
sarvapāpavimuktātmā śakraloke mahīyate|| 32.222||
tato gaṇapatiṃ tatra haribhadram ayojayat|
kālīṃ cāsmai dadau prītyā bhāryāṃ sarvaguṇoditām|| 32.223||
varāṃśca vipulān divyān dvīpaṃ cāpi ghṛtodakam|
bāhujebhyaśca subahūn gaṇebhyaḥ pradadau varān|| 32.224||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa dakṣayajño vai vidhvasto vyāsa śambhunā|
yajñasya ca śiraśchinnaṃ yathaitat kathitaṃ tava|| 32.225||
vyāsa uvāca|
sā devīmukhajā ghorā divyā devabhayaṃkarī|
kva vā gatā kathaṃ vāpi hyetadicchāmi veditum|| 32.226||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
stutā yadā bhagavatī praṇataiḥ surasattamaiḥ|
tadāsya sāmbikā prāha brūhi kiṃ karavāṇyaham|| 32.227||
tato brahmā mahādevīṃ praṇamya bahumānataḥ|
uvāca duhitṛtve me bhavatveṣā sureśvari|| 32.228||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam astvityumā procya tāṃ devīṃ pradadau sutām|
mṛtyustvam iti so 'apyuktvā ghore karmaṇyayojayat|| 32.229||
sarvaprāṇabṛtāṃ devīṃ prāṇāpaharaṇe śubhām|
sāpi tatkāryakaraṇe niyuktā brahmaṇā svayam|
ūrdhvabāhuḥ sadeveśā sadodyuktā tvayā mayā|| 32.230||
ya idaṃ dakṣayajñasya vidhvaṃsanamanuttamam|
bhadreśvarapratiṣṭhāṃ ca dakṣānugraham eva ca|| 32.231||
paṭhedvā śṛṇuyādvāpi śrāvayīta dvijānapi|
sa sarvapāpavirmuktaḥ svargaloke mahīyate|| 32.232||
bhaganayananipātaṃ dakṣayajñe davāgniṃ madanapurahutāśaṃ candralekhojjvalāṅgam|
suragurumakhakālaṃ saptalokādhipālaṃ śaraṇam upagato 'ahaṃ śaṃkaraṃ śarmahetoḥ|| 32.233||
iti skandapurāṇe
dakṣayajñapramathane dvātriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 32.32||

trayastriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
yathā tu vṛṣabho devam avahanmunipuṅgava|
tat te 'ahaṃ sampravakṣyāmi namaskṛtya vṛṣadhvajam|| 33.1||
pūrvam eva mahāsatvo dharmo yajñasahāyavān|
tatāpa vipulaṃ nyāsa tapaḥ paramaduścaram|| 33.2||
himavantaṃ giriṃ prāpya vāyvāhārau babhūvatuḥ|
varṣāṇāṃ tu sahasrāṇi daśa dvādaśa caiva tau|| 33.3||
māṇuṣāni tato bhūyaḥ śākāhārau babhūvatuḥ|
tato 'acirāt tayordevo gaṇaiḥ saha mahādyutiḥ|| 33.4||
sarvaiḥ samānarūpaistairdarśanaṃ pradadau haraḥ|
tāṃstau maheśvarān dṛṣṭvā bahūn vai sadṛśaprabhān|| 33.5||
parasparam amanyetāṃ ko nveṣām īśvaro bhavet|
tau tadā vīkṣya saṃmantrya smṛtvā caiva punaḥ punaḥ|| 33.6||
madhye maheśvaraṃ teṣāṃ menāte tejasāṃ nidhim|
tau taṃ madhye bhavaṃ devaṃ praṇamya bahumānataḥ|
śirasorañjalī kṛtvā tuṣṭuvāte 'amitaujasau|| 33.7||
dharmayajñaūcatus|
namastrailokyanāthāya digvāsāyāmṛtātmane|
catuṣpathanivāsāya catuṣpatharatāya ca|| 33.8||
caturvyūhāya devāya trinetrāya bhavāya ca|
caturmukhāya śuddhāya jālāntaravicāriṇe|| 33.9||
indrānugrahakartre ca brahmānugrahakāriṇe|
ūrdhvaliṅgāya devāya madanāyāmadāya ca|| 33.10||
namo hiraṇyavarṇāya sūryākṣāya tathaiva ca|
namaḥ pavitrakeśāya dīrghajihvāya caiva hi|| 33.11||
namaste naikapādāya ekākṣāya namo namaḥ|
namaḥ sahasraghaṇṭāya sahasrākṣāya vai namaḥ|| 33.12||
namaḥ pinākine caiva dhvajine ca namo namaḥ|
namaḥ sahasraśīrṣāya saṃvartāya namo namaḥ|| 33.13||
namaḥ stavyāya vai nityaṃ śatrughnāya namo namaḥ|
namo bhavāya bhavyāya bhāvanāya namo namaḥ|| 33.14||
namo varāya vai nityaṃ varadāya tathaiva ca|
gokarṇāya namo nityam aiśvaryapataye namaḥ|| 33.15||
namo 'astu viṣvaksenāya prabhāsāya namo namaḥ|
namo 'astu te 'annadāyaiva prāṇadāya namo 'astu te|| 33.16||
namaḥ pravartakāyaiva padmamālāya vai namaḥ|
namo mahārathāyaiva bhiravāya namo namaḥ|| 33.17||
namaścaturmukhāyaiva mahādevāya vai namaḥ|
namo 'astu brahmaṇe caiva dhruvāyaiva calāya ca|| 33.18||
namo 'astu nārīrūpāya subhagāya namo namaḥ|
madhyamāya namaste 'astu namaste sarvatastathā|| 33.19||
namo 'anumantā mantā tvaṃ sarvabhūtapravartakaḥ|
āvayorīpsitān kāmān vidhatsva bhuvaneśvara|| 33.20||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
yo 'anena stauti vai nityaṃ niyamena samanvitaḥ|
sarvakāmaiḥ sa sampanno yatheṣṭāṃ gatim āpnuyāt|| 33.21||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha devastu tān sarvānanayat prakṛtiṃ gaṇān|
nandinaṃ caiva devīṃ ca svayaṃ cātmānam apyuta|
uvāca caitau tuṣṭo 'asmi gṛhyatām īpsito varaḥ|| 33.22||
devaūcatuḥ|
yadi tuṣṭo 'asi deveśa yadi deyo varaśca nau|
jātyantaragatau nityaṃ vaheva tvāṃ sureśvara|| 33.23||
idaṃ ca guhyaṃ sthānaṃ nau tapasātīva bhāvitam|
tava caiva prasādena bhavet puṇyaṃ sureśvara|| 33.24||
devadeva uvāca|
idaṃ mama paraṃ guhyaṃ bhavitṛ sthānam uttamam|
pañceṣukṣepamātraṃ vai mṛgo 'atra gaṇapo bhavet|| 33.25||
yasmānmadhye bhavo 'asmīti yuvayorarcitaḥ sthitaḥ|
tasmānnāmnā tu vikhyātam idaṃ bhavatu madhyamam|| 33.26||
yuvāṃ jātyantaraṃ prāpya pūjitau balavattarau|
vāhanatvaṃ mamāsādya lokān sandhārayiṣyathaḥ|| 33.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tata evaṃ tadā devastāvuktvā devasattamau|
jagāma gaṇapaiḥ sārdhaṃ mandaraṃ hemakandaram|| 33.28||
gate 'atha deve sagaṇe kālena bahunā tataḥ|
manvantare 'asmin surabhī rudram ārādhayacchubhā|| 33.29||
tayā varṣasahasreṇa tapasā toṣito bhavaḥ|
jagāma darśanaṃ vyāsa varado 'asmīti cābravīt|| 33.30||
sā vavre putram atulaṃ sarvaprāṇabhṛtāṃ varaḥ|
putrāṃścānyān mahāsattvān yajñiyān surasattamān|| 33.31||
tathā duhitR̥ścānyāśca jagaddhartrīḥ suśobhanāḥ|
tataḥ sarvaṃ dadau devo hyadṛśyatvaṃ jagāma ca|| 33.32||
tasmin gate mahādeve surabhī dīptatejasam|
sarvabhūtāgrajaṃ putraṃ vṛṣabhaṃ samasūyata|| 33.33||
ekādaśa tathā rudrān vṛṣabhasyānujāñchubhān|
sapta kanyāśca tā gā vai jagaddhātrī prasūyata|| 33.34||
vṛṣabhaḥ sa tu saṃgatya nityaṃ prātaḥ kṛtāhnikaḥ|
pitaraṃ mātaraṃ caiva tathaiva ca pitāmaham|| 33.35||
abhivādyāyate śubhraścaturdiggajasevitam|
vanaṃ siddhagaṇāvāsaṃ yatra sā hyamṛtodbhavā|| 33.36||
dūrvāmṛtarasā divyā chinnadagdhaprasehaṇī|
sa kadrācidvane tasmiṃścaraṃstṛptastṛḍarditaḥ|| 33.37||
jagāma sāgaraṃ pātuṃ vṛṣarāṭ surabhīsutaḥ|
so 'avagāhya mahāgrāsaḥ sāgarasya tadā mahat|| 33.38||
madhyaṃ vyādāya vadanaṃ sajhaṣaṃ satimiṃgalam|
apibat sāgarajalaṃ na ca tṛptim upāgamat|| 33.39||
tasmin pibati daityendrāḥ sannaddhāḥ sāsimārgaṇāḥ|
sadhanuṣpāṇayaḥ sarve sahasrāṇi caturdaśa|| 33.40||
niṣpetuḥ śakrasaṃkāśā yamakālānalopamāḥ|
mayaputrā mahāsatvā vṛṣabhaṃ prati vegitāḥ|| 33.41||
tāṃstathā ruṣitān daityān sāsimudgaratomarān|
sahaiva sāgarāmbhobhirapibat sa mahābalaḥ|| 33.42||
tān pītān pīyamānāṃśca dṛṣṭvā hyarṇavavāsinaḥ|
vitresuḥ sahasā sarve vineduścāpi duḥkhitāḥ|| 33.43||
tataḥ samudro bhagavān pīyamānaḥ suduḥkhitaḥ|
vaḍavāmukham āgatya saṃvartaṃ śaraṇaṃ yayau|| 33.44||
sa cānalaḥ susaṃrabdho dattvā tasya mahābalaḥ|
abhayaṃ vṛṣam āgatya provācedaṃ kṛtāñjaliḥ|| 33.45||
saṃvartta uvāca|
sarvabhūtaśaraṇyo 'ayaṃ daityānāṃ cālayaḥ śubhaḥ|
nainaṃ hīnaṃ bhavānadbhiḥ kartum arhati vīryavān|| 33.46||
vṛṣabha uvāca|
na me matirabhūdagne niḥśeṣaṃ kartum ambudhim|
bhavāṃstvasya yato mantā kariṣye 'ahaṃ tato 'adya vai|| 33.47||
yaste darpaśca garvaśca yadbalaṃ yacca pauruṣam|
tanme darśaya havyeśa pibāmyenaṃ tavāgrataḥ|| 33.48||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā vṛṣendrastu vaḍavāmukhavāsinam|
saṃrambhāt sāgaraṃ pātuṃ niḥśeṣam upacakrame|| 33.49||
anala uvāca|
na me tvaṃ pratimaḥ śaktau na ca vairaṃ tvayā hi me|
yatra kṛtye 'aham ābaddhastat kariṣye tathā hyaham|| 33.50||
na tvaṃ pāsyasi rakṣiṣye sāgaraṃ mama sannidhau|
ahaṃ tvāṃ vārayiṣyāmi surabhīsuta katthana|| 33.51||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastaṃ bhagavān vahnirupaplutya mahādyutiḥ|
gale jagrāha balavān na cacāla tataḥ sa ca|| 33.52||
yat pītaṃ chardayāmāsa tat toyaṃ dānavairvinā|
audareṇāgninā tasya te dagdhāḥ sarva eva hi|| 33.53||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ saṃvartako vahnirnigṛhītaṃ kakudminam|
visṛjyovāca gaccheti na tvāṃ hanmi vṛṣeśvara|| 33.54||
śaktastavāhaṃ dahane hyaśakto me bhavān vadhe|
tathāpyahaṃ na garjāmi garjitaiḥ kiṃ balīyasām|| 33.55||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
visṛjya vṛṣabhaṃ vahnirāśu yātaḥ svam ālayam|
vṛṣabho 'api jagāmaiva duḥkhaśokābhisaṃvṛtaḥ|| 33.56||
so 'avamānena tejasvī mahokṣaḥ surabhīsutaḥ|
duḥkhena cābhisannātmā jagāmaivaṃ vicintayan|| 33.57||
abalo 'ahaṃ balī vahniryenāhaṃ nikṛtastathā|
jīviteśena (?) bhūtvā ca nāhaṃ prāṇairviyojitaḥ|| 33.58||
moghaṃ mama balaṃ sarvaṃ tathā caivābhigarjitam|
śarajjaladharasyeva vihīnasyādbhirambare|| 33.59||
adya prāṇānahaṃ tyakṣye niyato vratam āthitaḥ|
yathā na punarevaṃ me mānabhaṅgo bhaviṣyati|| 33.60||
śatruṇā nigṛhītasya durbalasya durātmanaḥ|
jīvitānmaraṇaṃ manye viśiṣṭaṃ jīvitena kim|| 33.61||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evaṃ cintayannukṣā vācaṃ śuśrāva khāc chubhām|
saurabheya na bhetavyaṃ yadbravīmi kuruṣva tat|| 33.62||
rudraṃ sarvasureśānaṃ sarvebhyo balavattaram|
taṃ prapadyasva deveśaṃ tato jeṣyasi pāvakam|| 33.63||
sa sraṣṭā sarvabhūtānāṃ brahmādīnāṃ na saṃśayaḥ|
sa te duḥkham idaṃ sarvaṃ vyapaneṣyati bho vṛṣa|| 33.64||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
etacchrutvā mahātejāḥ sādhyasya sumahātmanaḥ|
himavantaṃ giriṃ prāpya tatāpa vipulaṃ tapaḥ|| 33.65||
tasya vartṣasahasreṇa tatparasya tadāśiṣaḥ|
bhagavān sarvabhūteśaḥ sāmbaḥ sagaṇa ūcivān|| 33.66||
devadeva uvāca|
saurabheya mahābhāga tuṣṭo 'asmi tava putraka|
iṣṭān brūhi varān vatsa dāsye tān subahūnapi|| 33.67||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa devaṃ saṃdṛśya sāmbaṃ sagaṇam īśvaram|
praṇamya śirasā pādau prāñjaliḥ susamāhitaḥ|| 33.68||
bhūyo bhūyo nirīkṣyainaṃ praṇamya ca punaḥ punaḥ|
uvāca tapaso 'akṣayyam iccheyaṃ vai jagatpate|| 33.69||
balaṃ cānuttamaṃ deva yogaiśvaryaṃ tathākṣayam|
tvadīyo vāhanaścāham agninaivaṃ vimānitaḥ|| 33.70||
saṃvartakānalaṃ caiva vaḍavāmukhavāsinam|
draṣṭum icchāmi deveśa nigṛhītaṃ tvayāvyaya|| 33.71||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktastu tān dattvā varān satyavatīsuta|
vāmaṃ pārśvaṃ tathā mṛjya rudram ekaṃ sasarja ha|| 33.72||
kirīṭamālinaṃ tryakṣaṃ kuṇḍalāṅgadabhūṣaṇam|
mahoraskaṃ kavacinaṃ dhanurhastaṃ mahābalam|
baddhagodhāṅgulitraṃ ca khaṅgadivyāstradhāriṇam|| 33.73||
tam āha rudraṃ gaccheti vaḍavāmukhavāsinam|
saṃvarttakānalaṃ baddhvā visphurantam ihānaya|| 33.74||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vanditvā caraṇau tasya somasya gaṇanāyakaḥ|
jagāma sāgaraṃ vegāddadarśa ca hutāśanam|| 33.75||
sa yuddhaṃ balavat kṛtvā sughoraṃ lomaharṣaṇam|
saṃvarttakānalaṃ baddhvā devapārśvam upānayat|| 33.76||
vyāsa uvāca|
kīdṛk tadyuddham abhavadviṭpateḥ pāvakasya ca|
etadicchāmi vijñātuṃ vada tvaṃ vadatāṃ vara|| 33.77||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa gatvā gaṇapaḥ kruddhaḥ saṃvarttakam athānalam|
uvāca krodharaktākṣastadā vacanam arthavat|| 33.78||
gaṇapa uvāca|
svāmī sarvasya jagato devaścandrārdhabūṣaṇaḥ|
ājñāpayati vahne tvāṃ vṛṣam enaṃ prasādaya|| 33.79||
praṇato 'asmīti taṃ brūhi vṛṣabhaṃ sasuhṛjjanaḥ|
nideśe tiṣṭha caivāsya yat kartavyaṃ ca tat kuru|| 33.80||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam ukto 'analaḥ śrutvā devadevasya tadvacaḥ|
uvāca na tisaṃhṛṣṭastvidaṃ vacanam arthavat|| 33.81||
anala uvāca|
niyojyo devadevasya tasyaivāhaṃ sadānugaḥ|
na ca māṃ sa niyuktveha yokṣyate 'anyatra karhicit|| 33.82||
gaccha madvacanādbrūhi bhagavantaṃ trilocanam|
yadi māṃ vakṣyati punaḥ kariṣye 'ahaṃ tatastathā|| 33.83||
gaṇeśvara uvāca|
bāliśā vata ye prājñā balajñānabahiṣkṛtāḥ|
ta evam uktā gacchanti yathā māṃ tvaṃ prabhāṣase|| 33.84||
sakṛdājñā balavatāṃ sakṛt prabhavatām api|
dūtaścāpi sa vai śreṣṭho yo bhavedarthasādhakaḥ|| 33.85||
so 'ahaṃ balavatā tena lokakartrā pinākinā|
dūtaḥ sarvārthasiddhyarthaṃ prahito balavāniha|| 33.86||
na cedvaco me kartāsi baddhvā tvāhaṃ tato 'adya vai|
visphurantaṃ mahāpāśairneṣyāmi dyubhṛto 'antikam|| 33.87||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktastejasvī krodhadīptānalekṣaṇaḥ|
gaṇapaṃ prati dudrāva tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti cābravīt|| 33.88||
tam āpatantaṃ vegena parjanyāstreṇa so 'astravit|
tāḍayāmāsa balavān sa prajajvāla vegavān|| 33.89||
jvalantaṃ taṃ tadābhyāsam āgataṃ krodhamūrcchitam|
aśanyastreṇa mahatā sa jaghāna stanāntare|| 33.90||
abhyāhatastato 'astreṇa vegavānapi mūrcchitaḥ|
tasthau muhūrtaṃ saṃvigno vidhūmo dahaneśvaraḥ|| 33.91||
tatastaṃ rudrapāśena babandha karayostadā|
visphurantaṃ mahāvahniṃ gaṇapaḥ krodhamūrcchitaḥ|| 33.92||
taṃ baddhaṃ pāśavaryeṇa patitaṃ vīkṣya caiva hi|
tasya putrasuhṛdvargā vividhāyudhapāṇayaḥ|| 33.93||
dudruvurgaṇapaṃ kruddhāḥ śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|
tānapyasau vinirjitya gaṇapastaṃ hutāśanam|| 33.94||
upaninye harāyāśu paśuṃ medhyam ivādhvare|
tam ānītaṃ mahādevaḥ samprekṣyārṇavabhojanam|| 33.95||
uvāca vṛṣabhaṃ brūhi kim asya kriyatām iti|
sa taṃ kṛpaṇam ālakṣya mahokṣā dīnacetasam|| 33.96||
praṇamya śirasā pādāvidam āha kṛtāñjaliḥ|
bhagavan devadeveśa sarvalokamaheśvara|| 33.97||
dṛṣṭam etat tava vibho māhātmyaṃ sadasatpate|
dṛṣṭo 'ayaṃ kṛpaṇaścāpi hyabalaśca mahābala|| 33.98||
visṛjyatāṃ suraśreṣṭha hata eṣa na saṃśayaḥ|
putrā hyasya hatāḥ sarve suhṛdaścaiva sarvaśaḥ|| 33.99||
dīnasyāsya na me deva vadha iṣṭo vimucyatām|
etadvaco maheśo vai vṛṣabhasyāmibhāṣitam|| 33.100||
śrutvā tuṣṭaḥ prahasyainaṃ dahanaṃ vyasṛjat tadā|
rudraṃ taṃ ca jarāśokajanmamṛtyuvivarjitam|| 33.101||
gaṇeśvarapatiṃ kṛtvā dvīpam asmai dadat prabhuḥ|
manoramaṇam ityeva nāmnā khyātaṃ maharddhimat|| 33.102||
divyaṃ kāmagamaṃ vyāsa bhavanairupaśobhitam|
jāmbūnadamayaiḥ śubhraiḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaiḥ|| 33.103||
tasmin kāle tadā devyāḥ sarve brahmapuraḥsarāḥ|
devadevaṃ samāgamya vākyam ūcuryathārthavat|| 33.104||
bhagavan devatārighna vṛṣo 'ayaṃ devasattama|
tvayā hyadhyāsitaḥ pūrvaṃ nādenāpūrayadbalī|| 33.105||
trailokyam akhilaṃ darpādasvasthaṃ kṛtavān prabho|
vegena ca diśaḥ sarvā vimānaiḥ saha bhūtapa|| 33.106||
bhrāmayaṃstridaśān nādādgagane saṃcacāra ha|
adhunā varalabdhaśca asmān bhūyastathaiva ca|| 33.107||
yathā na kurute deva upāyaḥ sa vidhīyatām|
tvaṃ no gatiśca deveśa śaraṇaṃ caiva bhūtapa|
sadā bhayābhibhūtānāṃ tvaṃ trātā sarvaśaḥ prabho|| 33.108||
devadeva uvāca|
yathā bhayaṃ na bhavati yathā svasthāśca nityaśaḥ|
lokā bhavanti sarve vai tathāhaṃ vidadhāmi vaḥ|| 33.109||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān vyāsa devadevo mahādyutiḥ|
asṛjadvaradānācca gaṇeśaṃ cārukuṇḍalam|| 33.110||
ākarṇāddāritāsyaṃ ca mahākāyaṃ mahābalam|
mahāparighabāhuṃ ca vajrasaṃhananaṃ dṛḍham|| 33.111||
mahādaṃṣṭraṃ mahoraskaṃ mahākhaḍgadhanurdharam|
dīptāṅgārakanetraṃ ca trinetraṃ kavacojjvalam|| 33.112||
bibhrat taṃ cākṣayetyartham iṣudhī carmavāsasam|
śaram ekena hastena dhanurekena bibhratam|| 33.113||
grahanakṣatracitreṇa taḍitsūryāvabhāsitā|
uttarīyeṇa viyatā bhāsvantaṃ merukūṭavat|| 33.114||
prabhākareti suvyaktam āmantrya bhagavānidam|
abravīt sarvadevānāṃ samakṣaṃ taṃ prabhākaram|| 33.115||
prabhākara mayājñaptastvaṃ devānāṃ guṇākara|
paramaiśvaryasaṃyukto vṛṣavegaṃ nivāraya|| 33.116||
jyotsnā bhavitrī patnī te tathā caivājarāmaraḥ|
bhaviṣyasi mayājñapto mahāgaṇapatirmama|| 33.117||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastaṃ devatāḥ sarvāḥ praṇamya brahmaṇā saha|
jagmuḥ svāni kṣayāni sma devo 'api vṛṣavān babhau|| 33.118||
mukhato 'ardhaṃ vṛṣo dharmo jaghanaṃ yajña ucyate|
cakṣuṣī candrasūryau ca brahmā mūrdhānam āśritaḥ|| 33.119||
jihvāyāṃ tasya varuṇo vāyurantaścaraḥ svayam|
pādān viṣṇurbhagaścaiva pūṣā śakraśca saṃsthitāḥ|| 33.120||
jaṃghāḥ śeṣāstathā divyā ūrūścaiva samāśritāḥ|
rudrāḥ karṇau ca nāsāṃ ca grīvoṣṭhau hanum eva ca|| 33.121||
āyudhāni khurāstasya cakravajrau ca śṛṅgayoḥ|
apāne ca svayaṃ mitraḥ pucchaṃ dānāni sarvaśaḥ|| 33.122||
asthīni parvatāḥ sarve purīṣaṃ śrīrabhūcchubhā|
mūtraṃ cāsyābhavaddivyam amṛtaṃ vyāsa pāvanam|| 33.123||
romāṇi ṛṣayaḥ sarve nakṣatrāṇi ca sarvaśaḥ|
grahāstasyābhavan vyāsa sandhayaḥ śubhadarśanāḥ|| 33.124||
iṣṭayo vedayajñāśca mantrāḥ stotrāḥ phalāni ca|
abhavaṃstasya māṃsāni rudhiraṃ saridarṇavāḥ|| 33.125||
saptalokaṃ mukhaṃ hi āsīt tasyāpratimatejasaḥ|
hantā marīcayaścaiva majjā auṣadhya eva ca|| 33.126||
mantrabhūtāśca paśavaḥ sakṛt (?) snāyuśca vīrudhaḥ|
ballyo 'atha vṛkṣagulmāśca tathaivānye nagāḥ śubhāḥ|| 33.127||
nāgāstasyābhavan nāḍyo vasavaḥ śukrasaṃcayaḥ|
āmapakvāśayau tasya tau devāvaśvinau smṛtau|| 33.128||
meghāstasyābhavaṃstvak ca taḍinmālā -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- yakṣā gandharvāpsarasastathā|| 33.129||
śirā dhamanyo 'atha mado darpāścaivābhijajñire|
mānuṣā mātaraścaiva bhūtāni vividhāni ca|| 33.130||
romakūpāṇi tasyāsan vṛṣabhasya mahātmanaḥ|
evaṃ sa bhagavān devaḥ paramaiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|
saurabheyo mahādevaḥ sarvadevamayo 'abhavat|| 33.131||
ya idaṃ saurabheyasya janma karma ca tattvataḥ|
mahātyam akhilaṃ caiva śṛṇuyādvā paṭheta vā|| 33.132||
nityaṃ śuciradīnātmā sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
mṛtaśca kāle kāle vā rudralokam avāpnuyāt|| 33.133||
nedaṃ śaṭhāya dātavyaṃ śrāvyaṃ vāpi kathaṃcana|
na nāstikāya duṣṭāya tathā vā pāpakarmaṇe|| 33.134||
idaṃ putraya śiṣyāya dhārmikāya mahātmane|
deyaṃ śrāvyaṃ ca śucaye guhyam etat sanātanam|| 33.135||
yo lokavedaprabhavena tena sarvārthasiddhena mahābalena|
yātyambudāmbhonidhirgarjitena sa vo 'astu nityaṃ sumanā maheśaḥ|| 33.136||
iti skandapurāṇe
vṛṣotpattimāhātmyaṃ nāma trayastriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 33.33||

catustriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa bhagavān vyāsa megham utsṛjya devapaḥ|
vṛṣavāhaḥ samabhavadyathā te kathitaṃ mayā|| 34.1||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ bhagavatī devī kṛṣṇā gauratvam āgatā|
kāraṇaṃ tatra kiṃ cāpi hyetadicchāmi veditum|| 34.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
āsīnau mandaraprasthe umākāmāṅganāśanau|
remāte pramathaiḥ sārdhaṃ nānārūpadharaistadā|| 34.3||
atha devena tatrasthā krīḍatā sā kathāntare|
kṛṣṇetyuktā bhagavatī sā cukopa manasvinī|| 34.4||
kupitāṃ tāṃ mahādevaḥ pariṣvajya mahādyutiḥ|
uvācāsakṛdavyagraḥ sāntvayan madhuraṃ vacaḥ|| 34.5||
devadeva uvāca|
deva mā krodham anaghe kṛthā viśvasṛgavyaye|
hāsyaṃ prakṛtam etanme kṛṣṇeti samudāhṛtam|| 34.6||
adya prabhṛti nānena vacasāhaṃ śubhānane|
vakṣyāmi tvāṃ tyaja krodhaṃ tām uvāca pinākadhṛk| 7||

pañcatriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaḥ sukeśaṃ gaṇapaṃ punaḥ|
cakāra brāhmaṇaṃ vyāsa tapaḥsatyaparāyaṇam|| 35.1||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ sa brāhmaṇaḥ pūrvaṃ gaṇeśatvam upāgataḥ|
kenāsya tapasā tuṣṭo gaṇeśatvaṃ dadau prabhuḥ|| 35.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
āsīdvasiṣṭhakulajo brāhmaṇaḥ satyavāk śuciḥ|
tīrthayātrāsvabhirata upavāsaparāyaṇaḥ|| 35.3||
sa kadācidvideśastho vane 'apaśyat pathi sthitam|
vyāghraṃ vyāttānanaṃ ghoraṃ nakhadaṃṣṭrāyudhaṃ tadā|| 35.4||
dṛṣṭvā taṃ sa tadā viprastyaktvā panthānam āśugaḥ|
viveśa mahatīṃ ghorām aṭavīṃ prāṇivarjitām|| 35.5||
tatrāpaśyat sa purato vīraṇastambam āśritān|
puruṣā/llambamānāṃśca krandamānān suduḥkhitān|| 35.6||
tānavākśiraso dṛṣṭvā lambamānāṃstadā dvijān|
ke yūyam iti papraccha te cainam idam ūcire|| 35.7||
pitara ūcuḥ|
tava smaḥ pitaraḥ sarve narake 'asminnadhomukhāḥ|
vīraṇe tvayi lambāmastava doṣeṇa durmate|| 35.8||
putrānicchanti manujāstārayiṣyanti anstvime|
narakāditi sa tvaṃ naḥ pātayiṣyasi duḥkhitān|| 35.9||
vipra uvāca|
mayā tīrthābhigamanāt tapo yat samupārjitam|
janmaprabhṛti yaccāpi mayā kiṃcit kṛtaṃ śubham|
tena yūyam ito garttāduddharadhvaṃ pitāmahāḥ|| 35.10||
pitara ūcuḥ|
na vayaṃ tapasā śakyā nayajñairnāpyato 'anyathā|
garttādasmāt samuddhartuṃ yadbrūmastat kuruṣva naḥ|| 35.11||
apatyaṃ guṇasaṃyuktam utpādaya tapoyutam|
tato vayam ito garttānmucyema yadi manyase|| 35.12||
vipra uvāca|
ūrdhvaretāham ityetanmayā vrtam upākṛtam|
na dārān āhariṣyāmi tārayiṣye ca vai pitR̥n|| 35.13||
tataḥ sa tāṃstathotsṛjya duḥkhena mahatā vṛtaḥ|
jagāma rudraṃ śaraṇaṃ pitaro 'antarhitāstataḥ|| 35.14||
pitṛṣvantarhiteṣvevaṃ vāyubhakṣastadā dvijaḥ|
kāṣṭhaloṣṭhopalībhūto nirucchvāso 'avatiṣṭhata|| 35.15||
sandhāya mānasaṃ rudre niścalaḥ susamāhitaḥ|
hṛdayena japan rudrān ākāśe samatiṣṭhata|| 35.16||
tasya pūrṇe tadā māsi vātavarṣam abhūnmahat|
sarvasattvapramathanaṃ duḥsahaṃ bhīmaśabdavat|| 35.17||
tena varṣeṇa mahatā naiva tasyābhavat tadā|
duḥkhaṃ vāpi athavā bhaṅgaḥ samyagevāvatasthivān|| 35.18||
atha taṃ bhagavān devo māse vartati saptame|
viṣṇurūpadharo bhūtvā provāca dvijasattamam|| 35.19||
tuṣṭo 'asmi tava bhadraṃ te tapasānena suvrata|
varaṃ varaya viprarṣe yaste manasi vartate|| 35.20||
sukeśastu tato dṛṣṭvā nārāyaṇam upāgatam|
abravīcchaṃkarādicche varaṃ na bhavato hyaham|| 35.21||
viṣṇuruvāca|
alam etena viprarṣe nirbandhena haraṃ prati|
devairapi na śakyo 'asau draṣṭuṃ kim uta mānuṣaiḥ|| 35.22||
sukeśa uvāca|
draṣṭuṃ śakyo na vā śakyaḥ kim ebhirvo vicāritaiḥ|
kugrahaḥ sugraho vāhaṃ tathāpīśe mānrmama|| 35.23||
śaṃkarādeva cakreśa śubhaṃ vā yadi vāśubham|
varaṃ kāṃkṣe na ca tvatto na cānyasmāt kathaṃcana|| 35.24||
bhavanto 'api hi taṃ devaṃ yasmāt sarve samāhitāḥ|
arcayadhve stuvadhve ca tasmācchreṣṭhaḥ sa ucyate|| 35.25||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya taṃ niścayaṃ jñātvā saṃtuṣṭo bhagavān haraḥ|
viṣṇurūpaṃ parityajya svaṃ rūpaṃ pratyapadyata|| 35.26||
uvāca cainaṃ viprendra gaṇapo me bhavākṣayaḥ|
amaro jarayā tyaktaḥ sarvaduḥkhavivarjitaḥ|| 35.27||
aiśvaryeṇa ca saṃyuktaḥ priyo mama puraḥsaraḥ|
imaṃ ca matkṛtaṃ divyaṃ trikūṭaṃ nāma parvatam|| 35.28||
bhavanaiḥ kāñcanairyuktaṃ kāmagaṃ te dadāmyaham|
yeṣāṃ kṛte ca putra tvaṃ māṃ toṣayitum udyataḥ|| 35.29||
te ceme pitaraḥ sarve suputreṇa tvayānagha|
tāritā narakādghorādgaṇeśaṃ tvām upasthitāḥ|| 35.30||
kiṃkarāste bhaviṣyanti nityaṃ duḥkhavivarjitāḥ|
gaṇeśvarāstavaiveme bhaviṣyanti vaśānugāḥ|| 35.31||
sukeśa iti nāmnā ca prathitastvaṃ bhaviṣyasi|
sadā cāṣṭaguṇaiśvaryasamāyuktaścariṣyasi|| 35.32||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa dṛṣṭvātha pitR̥n narakāt sasuhṛjjanān|
tīrṇān gaṇeśvaratvena punaḥ pūjyena saṃyutān|| 35.33||
maheśvaraṃ hṛṣṭamanāḥ śirasā prāñjalirnataḥ|
uvāca hṛṣyamāṇāsyastadā vacanakovidaḥ|| 35.34||
sukeśa uvāca|
bhagavan gaṇapatvaṃ ca labdham aiśvaryam eva ca|
amaratvaṃ tathākṣayyaṃ tathaivājaratā varā|| 35.35||
pitarastāritāśceme gaṇapāścaiva me kṛtāḥ|
nagaśca kāmago hyeṣa labdho me tvatprasādataḥ|| 35.36||
icchāmi tvāṃ mahādeva somaṃ sapravareśvaram|
sadā sumukham atyarthaṃ sudṛśyaṃ caiva kāmada|| 35.37||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto bhagavān sukeśena mahātmanā|
uvācaivam idaṃ sarvaṃ bhaviṣyati gaṇeśvara|| 35.38||
imaṃ giriṃ samāśritya sahaibhiḥ pravarairvaraiḥ|
gaccha sveṣṭāṃ gatiṃ vatsa devān viprāṃśca pālaya|| 35.39||
visṛjya taṃ tato devaḥ sukeśaṃ gaṇanāyakam|
jagāmādarśanaṃ somaḥ sarveṣām eva paśyatām|| 35.40||
sukeśo 'api girau tasmin nagare svargasannibhe|
narakāṇāṃ sa tattvārthaṃ pitR̥n papraccha yatnataḥ|| 35.41||
vyāsa uvāca|
kimarthaṃ gaṇapo brahmaṃstān pitR̥n paryapṛcchata|
kathaṃ ca pitarastatra ācakhyustasya dhīmataḥ|| 35.42||
etadvistaraśastāta saṃkṣepādvā yathātatham|
tvatto 'ahaṃ śrotum icchāmi hitaṃ sarvasukhāvaham|| 35.43||
sūta uvāca|
sa evam uktaḥ surasṛksutaḥ prabhurvimānakartā vigataprayojanaḥ|
jagāda vākyaṃ suralokavardhanaḥ purā kṛtaṃ suṣkṛtasarvanāśanam|| 35.44|| (?)
iti skandapurāṇe sukeśavarapradānaṃ nāma
pañcatriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 35.35||

ṣaṭtriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
trikūṭaśikhare tasmin nagare devanirmite|
āsīnaḥ kāñcane divye vimāne strīsamākule|| 36.1||
pitR̥n sarvān samāhūya saṃpūjya vidhivat tadā|
sukhopaviṣṭāṃstān dṛṣṭvā idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 36.2||
sukeśa uvāca|
yuṣmākaṃ tejasā sarvam idam aiśvaryam īdṛśam|
bhavadbhistat kṛtaṃ devā yenāsmni sukhabhāk kṛtaḥ|| 36.3||
pitara ūcuḥ|
maivaṃ vadānṛtaṃ putra mādharmaste bhavediha|
nāsmatprasādādaiśvaryaṃ tava putra kadācana|| 36.4||
vayaṃ tu niraye ghore yātyamānāḥ sudāruṇe|
tapasā tava vīryeṇa sukham āpma sudurlabham|| 36.5||
tvayā vayaṃ suputreṇa tāritā nirayādyathā|
tathā nānyaṃ prapaśyāmo dhanyo hi tvaṃ suto hi naḥ|| 36.6||
adya varṣasahasrāṇi bahūni niraye vayam|
pacyema ghore durvṛttā bandhuḥ syāstvaṃ na no yadi|| 36.7||
bahavaḥ prāṇinaḥ putra yātyante tātra saṃyatāḥ|
atighore sudurvṛttāstapo yeṣāṃ na vidyate|| 36.8||
sukeśa uvāca|
pitaro noktapūrvaṃ me mṛṣā na ca vadāmi vai|
yathā prabhāvādyuṣmākam aiśvaryaṃ mama tat tadā|| 36.9||
śṛṇudhvaṃ vadataḥ samyaṅmāvamadhvaṃ vaco mama|
na cāvamanye pitaro devatāḥ ko 'avamanyate|| 36.10||
pitaraḥ karma kurvanti satāṃ yat saṃmataṃ bhuvi|
nityaṃ cāśāsate caiva prajā naḥ santu puṣkalāḥ|| 36.11||
dhārmikāśca kṛtajñāśca satkarmaratayastathā|
ye no narakagartasthāṃstārayisyanti nityaśaḥ|| 36.12||
teṣāṃ tatkāryakaraṇāt svadharmācyavanena ca|
sa dharmo 'anuṣṭhitaḥ samyak prajā janayate śubhāḥ|| 36.13||
dhārmikāśca vadanyāśca kṛtajñāḥ satpathe sthitāḥ|
pitṛbhaktāśca sarvatra pitR̥ṇāṃ tāraṇe ratāḥ|| 36.14||
so 'ahaṃ bhavadbhirdharmeṇa pareṇa ca samādhinā|
janitastapasā yukto bhavatām eva sarvaśaḥ|| 36.15||
devam ārādhya narakāt pitR̥ṃstāritavān punaḥ|
eṣa prabhāvo yuṣmākaṃ tapaḥ sucaritaṃ ca ha|| 36.16||
mamātra kiṃ mahāprajñā anṛtaṃ vātra kiṃ vacaḥ|
iyaṃ ca vaidikī śubhrā śritirvedavidāṃ varāḥ|| 36.17||
pramāṇaṃ yadi manyadhva ātmanā kṛtam ityuta|
aṅgādaṅgāt saṃbhavasi hṛdayādadhijāyase|| 36.18||
ātmā vai putranāmāsi sa jīva śaradāṃ śatam|
aṅgebhyo 'ahaṃ samutpanno yuṣmākaṃ hṛdayācca ha|| 36.19||
ātmanāhaṃ tathātmānaṃ yuṣmāṃstāritavāṃstataḥ|
tasmādbhavanto manyantāṃ sarva eva samādhinā|| 36.20||
tasmāddhi ghorānnarakāt tāritāḥ svena karmaṇā|
na cānyakarmaṇā kaścidanyastarati durmatiḥ|
svakarmaṇā hi jantūnāṃ phalapāko vidhīyate|| 36.21||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatasta evaṃ pitarastena proktā mahātmanā|
harṣeṇa sāśrunayanā idam ūcustadā vacaḥ|| 36.22||
pitara ūcuḥ|
tvadanyaḥ ko vadedevaṃ yo na syādīśasaṃmataḥ|
yuktam etat tava vaco dhārmikasya mahātmanaḥ|| 36.23||
yo na syādīdṛśaḥ putra kathaṃ taṃ sarvadevapaḥ|
iṣṭaistu yojayet samyagyathā tvāṃ govṛṣadhvajaḥ|| 36.24||
tvaṃ dhātā tvaṃ hi no bandhustvaṃ janetā mahāmate|
pitā tvam eva putrā hi vayaṃ tava na saṃśayaḥ|| 36.25||
atra te tarpayiṣyāmaḥ purāvṛttaṃ mahāmate|
śrutau smṛtau ca yadgītaṃ tannastvaṃ mantum arhasi|| 36.26||
pitara ūcuḥ|
putrā hi brahmaṇā sṛṣṭā devā yajata mām iti|
te yajanta tadātmānaṃ teṣāṃ brahmā cukopa ha|| 36.27||
uvāca cainān saṃrabdho naṣṭasaṃjñā bhaviṣyatha|
te śaptā brahmaṇā sarve sametya ca divaukasaḥ|| 36.28||
duḥkhaśokasamāyuktā dīnāstaṃ tuṣṭuvustadā|
prasannaṃ taṃ samālakṣya ta ūcuḥ śirasā natāḥ|| 36.29||
naṣṭasaṃjñā vayaṃ deva tān no yaccha punaḥ prabho|
tat kṣamasva ca deveśa ajñānādyat kṛtaṃ hi naḥ|| 36.30||
athaivam ukto devaistairbrahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
uvāca praṇatān devān sānukrośam idaṃ vacaḥ|| 36.31||
brahmovāca|
prāyaścittaṃ mahāsattvāścaradhvaṃ niyamena ha|
vyabhicārakṛtaṃ sarvaṃ tataḥ pāpaṃ prahāsyatha|| 36.32||
devā ūcuḥ|
saiva saṃjñā na no deva vidyate sarvasṛk prabho|
yayā jñāsyāmahe tāni prāyaścittāni lokapa|| 36.33||
brahmovāca|
svān putrān paripṛcchadhvaṃ tataḥ śreyam avāpsyatha|
punaḥ saṃjñāṃ ca dharmajñā mā kurudhvam ato 'anyathā|| 36.34||
pitara ūcuḥ|
tataste suraśārdūlāḥ papracchuḥ svān sutāṃstadā|
prāyaścittāni dharmāṃśca vedān sāṅgān savistarān|| 36.35||
te ca tebhyastadā putrā ācakhyuḥ prayatāḥ śubhāḥ|
yātātahyena tat sarvaṃ parameṇa samādhinā|| 36.36||
atha te labdhasaṃjñāśca labdhakāmāstathaiva ca|
svān putrānabhyabhāṣanta prīyamāṇā mudā yutāḥ|| 36.37||
devā ūcuḥ|
putrā na yūyam asmākaṃ vayaṃ putrā hi vaḥ sutāḥ|
yairjñānaṃ naṣṭasaṃjñānāṃ kṛtam asmākam avyayam|| 36.38||
tairevam ukte tatrāgādbrahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
uvāca cedaṃ tān devān sarvāneva mahāyaśāḥ|| 36.39||
brahmovāca|
vadanti nānṛtaṃ devāḥ satyaṃ deveṣu vartate|
sutāścoktā hi vaḥ sarve pitaro nānṛtaṃ hi tat|| 36.40||
tasmāt pitṛtvaṃ yuṣmākaṃ putrāṇāṃ nityam avyayam|
bhaviṣyati na sandeho yūyaṃ putrāśca sarvaśaḥ|| 36.41||
na hyaśiṣyāya kathyante rahasyāni kathaṃcana|
ekārthau putraśiṣyau ca tasmāt putrāḥ stha sarvaśaḥ|| 36.42||
taranti putraiḥ pitaraḥ putrāṃstāṃstārayanti ca|
tārayitvā pitṛtvaṃ ca karmaṇā tena yānti te|| 36.43||
yūyaṃ ca tāritāḥ putrairajñānānnarakāt tathā|
tasmādime hi pitaro yūyaṃ putrāśca sarvaśaḥ|| 36.44||
pāti yasmāt pitā tasmājjanayatyapi vā pitā|
putreṣu caitadubhayaṃ pitarastena vo matāḥ|| 36.45||
tataste brahma-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 36.46||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- balāḥ|
pitarastān varairiṣṭaiśchandayāmāsuravyathāḥ|| 36.47||
pitaraśca tato vavruragre yajanam ātmanaḥ|
yo no 'aniṣṭvā yajeddevān na sa tatphalam āpnuyāt|| 36.48||
enasā cābhisaṃukto maha-- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 36.49||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
yathāgataṃ tato jagmurbrahmaṇā saha sarvaśaḥ|| 36.50||
pitara ūcuḥ|
yathā vayaṃ tvayā putra narakānnaṣṭacetasaḥ|
tāritāścetanāvantaḥ punaśca pravarīkṛtāḥ|| 36.51||
pitā tato bhavān pūjyo yo 'anuyāsi mahā-- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 36.52||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- sattamaḥ|
praṇataḥ prāñjalirbhūtvā pitR̥n vacanam abravīt|| 36.53||
evam etadyathoktaṃ vo nānṛtaṃ vo vacaḥ śubham|
parasparapitṛtvaṃ hi sarveṣāṃ samudāhṛtam|| 36.54||
varaṃ bhūya imaṃ mahyaṃ prayacchata gaṇeśvarāḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
etena praśnam iṣṭaṃ hi kathitaṃ dvijasattama (?)|| 36.55||
pitara ūcuḥ|
nāsti kiṃcidaviditaṃ bhavataḥ pravareśvara|
bhavānasmatpramāṇārthaṃ vyākhyātattvam ihecchasi|| 36.56||
brūhi yadviditaṃ no 'asti kathāyiṣyāma taddhi te|
śrutaṃ vāpyanubhūtaṃ va yathāśakti yathātatham|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 36.57||
sukeśa uvāca|
bhavanto narake ghore parikliṣṭāḥ sudāruṇe|
ataḥ śrutijñāḥ sarveṣāṃ narakāṇām asaṃśayaṃ || 36.58||
teṣāṃ satattvaṃ yogaṃ ca kālabhedaṃ tathā kramam|
tat sarvaṃ śrotum icchāmi paraṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me|| 36.59||
kiyanto narakāste ca kimpramāṇāḥ kimāśrayāḥ|
kiṃrūpāḥ ke ca yātyante kathaṃ caiva suduḥkhitāḥ|| 36.60||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 36.61||
kathaṃ ca tapyate janturvācyate (?) ca kathaṃ tathā|
kiyatā caiva kālena narakāt sa vimucyate|
muktaścottiṣṭhate kena kathaṃ saṃsarate punaḥ|| 36.62||
etat sarvam aśeṣena vistareṇa yathātatham|
kathayadhvaṃ mahāprajñāḥ paraṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me|| 36.63||
tam upendrapitāmaheśvareśapravareśaṃ viditārthatattvakośam|
duritāṅkita-- -- muktayogaṃ pratiyogaṃ tvidam āhuragrayogam|| 36.64||
iti skandapurāṇe sukeśamahābhāgyaṃ nāma
ṣaṭtriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 36.35||

saptatriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste pitarastasya pratiṣṭhāṃ svasutaṃ prati|
suśarmāṇam iti khyātaṃ kathayāmāsuravyayāḥ|| 37.1||
pitara ūcuḥ|
ayaṃ te janakaḥ putra suśarmā lokaviśrutaḥ|
kathāyiṣyati tattvena yat tvayā samudāhṛtam|| 37.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ suśarmā viprarṣe tam āmantrya mahāmanāḥ|
uvācedaṃ mahāsattvaṃ sukeśaṃ gaṇasattamam|| 37.3|\
suśarmovāca|
sukeśa na vayaṃ sākṣāt patitā narakārṇave|
tvayi ālambitacittastu patiṣyāmastvayā vinā|| 37.4||
kiṃ tu tadyātanābhītāścintayāmastvaharniśam|
kīdṛśāste mahāghorā narakāḥ śrutidāruṇāḥ|| 37.5||
tataste kathayiṣyāma yathāprajñaṃ yathāśrutam|
gaṇeśvareśa śṛnu me narakā ye prakīrtitāḥ|| 37.6||
durāsadā mahādurgāḥ sarvaprāṇibhayaṃkarāḥ|
prathamo narakastatra viśruto yamalācalaḥ|| 37.7||
dvitīyaḥ śālmalo nāma tṛtīyaḥ kālasūtrakaḥ|
kumbhīpākaścaturthaśca asipatravano 'aparaḥ|| 37.8||
tathā vaitaraṇī ṣaṣṭhaḥ saptamaścāpyayodhanaḥ|
aṣṭamaḥ padma ityeva mahāpadmastathāparaḥ|| 37.9||
rauravo daśamaścaiva mahāraurava eva ca|
dvadaśaśca tamo nāma tamastamatarastathā|| 37.10||
ete mahānto narakā ucchrāyāśca tathāpare|
ekaikasyocchrayā hyaṣṭau narakāste 'api kīrtitāḥ|| 37.11|
ucchrayeṣu saviśrāmā yātanā bhavatīśvara|
itareṣu tvaviśrāmo viśeṣo hyeṣa kīrtitaḥ|| 37.12||
teṣāṃ satataduḥkhaṃ tu nR̥ṇāṃ pāpena karmaṇā|
bhedaḥ kṣayācca pāpasya kramasteṣāṃ pravakṣyate|| 37.13||
pramāṇaṃ tu gaṇeśeha na śakyaṃ vaktum ekaśaḥ|
vibhutvāt karmaṇastasya kṣayādantaṃ prapaśyati|| 37.14||
narake patitaḥ sarvo nāntaṃ tasya prapaśyati|
kṣīṇapāpāḥ prapaśyanti yathā tacchṛṇu me 'avyaya|| 37.15||
patito narake ghore duṣkṛtī svena karmaṇā|
yātyamāno 'atikaruṇaṃ diśam ekāṃ prapadyate|| 37.16||
sa gatvā śīghram adhvānaṃ bahuyojanavistṛtam|
bahūnanyānanāsādya tasyāntaṃ vinivartate|| 37.17||
vinivṛtya tato bhūyo yātyamāno vicetanaḥ|
anyāṃ diśaṃ punargatvā tathaiva vinivartate|| 37.18||
evaṃ sarvā diśo gatvā hyantam aprāpya duḥkhitaḥ|
yātyate karuṇaṃ tatra na kaścidiha vidyate|| 37.19||
yātanānte tvakaruṇaṃ pāpasyānte tataḥ punaḥ|
prapaśyate parimitaṃ paricchinnaṃ ca sarvaśaḥ|| 37.20||
dvāreṇa mahatā yuktaṃ tatastasmādvimucyate|
evaṃ hi narakāḥ sarve hyanantāścākṣayāvyayāḥ|| 37.21||
na teṣāṃ parisaṃkhyānaṃ yojanaiḥ saṃvidhīyate|
yena kālena tu punarjantuḥ patati duḥkhitaḥ|| 37.22||
yathā caitacchṛṇu vibho kathyamānaṃ mayānagha|
kṛtvā pāpāni karmāṇi kṣayānte duṣṭacetanaḥ|| 37.23||
vyādhyādhiyuktaḥ kleśena tyajati svāṃstanūṃstataḥ|
yamadūtairmahāpāśairbaddhvā duḥkhasamīritaḥ|| 37.24||
viṣameṇa pathā deva nīyate vikṛtākṛtiḥ|
ayomayaiḥ kaṇṭakaiśca vidhyamānastatastataḥ|| 37.25||
keśamajjāsthipaṅkaiśca dihyamānaḥ samantataḥ|
viṣameṣu ca garteṣu prapatan bhidyate punaḥ|| 37.26||
kvaciccopalavarṣeṇa mahatā sannikīryate|
tatra bhinnaśirojānupādabāhūrubandhanaḥ|| 37.27||
kṛṣyate yamadūtaiśca punaḥ kaṇṭakibhirdrumaiḥ|
yātyate bhidyate caiva vallībhiścāvabaddhyate|| 37.28||
evaṃ bahuvidhākārairduḥkhadaiḥ pathibhiḥ prabho|
nīyamāno vaśaḥ kleśān prāpnoti yamasādanam|| 37.29||
sa tato yamam aprāpya dūrādeva yamājñayā|
citraguptam upāgamya śrāvyate karma yat kṛtam|| 37.30||
somo 'agnirvaruṇo vāyuḥ sūryaśceti tadā naram|
sākṣiṇastatra jantūnāṃ bruvate yat kṛtākṛtam|| 37.31||
ukto vibhāvitaścaiva citraguptena coditaḥ|
narake pātyate ārtta ūrdhvapādo hyadhaḥśirāḥ|| 37.32||
tomaraiścātitīkṣṇāgraiḥ śaraiścātha paraśvadhaiḥ|
bhindipālairmudgaraiśca asibhirdīghavedhanaiḥ|| 37.33||
parighaiḥ karapatraiśca vajraiḥ ṭaṃkairhalopalaiḥ|
kīlaiśca muśalaiścaiva kṣārapiṣṭena caiva hi|| 37.34||
pradīptaiścāyudhairghorairagnivarṣeṇa cāpyuta|
hanyamāno divārātraṃ vinadan karuṇaṃ bahu|| 37.35||
varṣāṇāṃ tu sahasreṇa narakaṃ prāpnute 'aśubham|
sa tatra patito bhūyo yātyamānaḥ suduḥkhitaḥ|| 37.36||
varṣakoṭim aviśrāntaṃ nirayāntaṃ prapadyate|
mahānarakamuktaśca ucchrayāntaram āśritaḥ|| 37.37||
śītena vāyunā spṛṣṭaḥ sukhaṃ tatra sa vindati|
sa taṃ viśrāmam āsādya vismṛto yātanāṃ tadā|| 37.38||
muhūrtam āhṛte svapne rākṣasenāpakṛṣyate|
sa tena kṛṣyamāṇaśca bhūyo duḥkhaśucārditaḥ|| 37.39||
karuṇaṃ bahudhātīva pravilapyāvatiṣṭhate|
tato bhūyaḥ samākṛṣya yātanāyāṃ sa rākṣasaḥ|| 37.40||
yātayatyeva taṃ jantuṃ saviśrāmaṃ sacetanam|
tatra varṣasahasraṃ vai yātitaḥ punareva ca|| 37.41||
anyasminnucchraye ghore yātyate tāvadeva hi|
evaṃ sa ucchrayān prāpya aṣṭau pāpena karmaṇā|| 37.42||
saṃsāre kṛmikīṭādijantuḥ sampratipadyate|
ye tu gacchanti tān ghorān narakān puruṣādhamāḥ|| 37.43||
tānahaṃ sampravakṣyāmi tava putra samāsataḥ|
prathamo yo mayā prokto narako yamalācalaḥ|| 37.44||
yātyante tatra puruṣā mahānirayagāminaḥ|
parvatau dvau mahāsattvasiṃhavyāghrasamākulau|| 37.45||
śarabhebhasamākīrṇau bahusarpasamākulau|
pakṣibhirvividhākāraiḥ puruṣaiścodyatāyudhaiḥ|| 37.46||
vṛkṣairaparṇaiḥ saṃyuktau sucībhirvajrakaṇṭakaiḥ|
tayorantaram ekaṃ vai samaṃ sūcībhirāvṛtam|| 37.47||
ūrdhvābhirvajratuṇḍābhirabhedyābhistathaiva ca|
anyataḥ puruṣairghoraiḥ śastrapāṇibhirāvṛtau|| 37.48||
prākāreṇa ca lauhena samantāt parivāritau|
ākāśe cāpi lauhena tau jālena samāvṛtau|| 37.49||
yātyante tatra puruṣā ye vai striyam anicchatīm|
ākramanti parakyāṃ vai kanyādūṣaka eva ca|| 37.50||
nyāsāpahārakaścaiva tathā māṃsāpahārakaḥ|
rasāpahārakaścaiva yaścāpi paradūṣakaḥ|| 37.51||
indriyagrāmaghātī ca mithyāliṅgī tathaiva ca|
mṛgaśvāpadahantā ca pṛṣṭhamāṃsāśinaśca ye|| 37.52||
vṛthāmāṃsāśino ye ca hiṃsāṃ ye ca prakurvate|
ete narādhamāḥ putra gacchanti yamalācalam|| 37.53||
yamaleṣu ca jāteṣu yo na kuryānnarādhamaḥ|
prāyaścittam aśuddhātmā sa ca taṃ pratipadyate|| 37.54||
sa prasanno yathoktaistaiḥ puruṣaiḥ samabhidrutaḥ|
āyudhaiśchidyamānaśca parvataṃ taṃ prapadyate|| 37.55||
tatra vyāghraiśca kupitaiḥ śarabhaiśca tarakṣubhiḥ|
sarpairviḍālaiḥ patagairayastuṇḍaiśca bhakṣyate|| 37.56||
tairbhakṣyamāṇo yadi ca vṛkṣaṃ samadhirohati|
tatra taiḥ kaṇṭakaistīkṣṇairbhidyate pakṣibhiśca ha|| 37.57||
atha cet kandarāṃ tasya guhāṃ vā yātum icchati|
tatrāpi hyagninā dagdho duḥkhārto vinivartate|| 37.58||
atha cedantaraṃ ghoraṃ tayoḥ sampratipadyate|
tatra sūcībhiragrābhiḥ pādayorbhidyate naraḥ|| 37.59||
bhinnaṃ ca taṃ samālakṣya hyaśaktam apasarpaṇe|
samāgamamyācalau kṣipraṃ pīḍayetām atīva hi|| 37.60||
pīḍyamāno 'acalābhyāṃ sa yantreṇekṣuvadāturaḥ|
karuṇaṃ krandamānastu yātanāṃ tāṃ samaśnute|| 37.61||
bhakṣitasyātha bhinnasya viluptasya ca pakṣibhiḥ|
dagdhasya ca navaṃ bhūyaḥ śarīram abhijāyate|| 37.62||
evaṃ sa yātyamāno vai bahūnabdān suduḥkhitaḥ|
dvāraṃ labdhvā viniryāta ucchrāyeṣu nipātyate|| 37.63||
yamalācalam etam ugravegaṃ bahudhāpāpasametakarmayogam|
śṛṇuyādyo 'abhīkṣṇaśo 'ativegaṃ sa na yātyeva tam ugrapāpayogam|| 37.64||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane
yamalācalakathanaṃ nāma saptatriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ||

aṣṭatriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi śālmalīnarakaṃ punaḥ|
yātyante tatra puruṣāḥ subhṛśaṃ pāpakarmiṇaḥ|| 38.1||
śālmalīnāṃ sahasrāṇi bahūni pravareśvara|
uccāḥ sarvāśca tā ghorā bahuyojanavistṛtāḥ|| 38.2||
mahāśākhā mahāpatrā mahākaṇṭakasaṃyutāḥ|
lauhena mahatā caiva prākārenābhisaṃvṛtāḥ|| 38.3||
jālena mahatā sarvā upariṣṭāt samāvṛtāḥ
puruṣāstatra tiṣṭhanti bahavo ruṣitānanāḥ|| 38.4||
vajradaṇḍopaladharā asimudgaradhāriṇaḥ|
anyaiśca vividhākārairāyudhairvṛtapāṇayaḥ|| 38.5||
yātayanti bhṛśaṃ jantūnavaśāste sudāruṇāḥ|
chidyamānaśca tatrāpi rākṣasaiḥ krūrakarmabhiḥ|| 38.6||
diśaḥ prapadyate sarvā vedanārtaḥ suduḥkhitaḥ|
vrajate yatra yatrāsau tatra tatrābhihanyate|| 38.7||
garteṣu partitaṃ caiva rākṣasāḥ prāpta sarvaśaḥ|
śastraiśca vividhākārairnikṛntantyatidāruṇāḥ|| 38.8||
śrāvayantaḥ purānena kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ durātmanā|
bhartsayantaśca durvṛttaṃ patitaṃ kvacideva hi|| 38.9||
tata utthāya bhinnāṅgaḥ so 'anubaddhaśca rākṣasaiḥ|
sūcīkaṇṭakasaṃyuktaṃ deśam anyaṃ prapadyate|| 38.10||
tatra sūcībhirugrābhiḥ kaṇṭakaiścāyasaiḥ punaḥ|
bhidyamāno nadan duḥkhānnipatatyatiduḥkhitaḥ|| 38.11||
tatrāpyenaṃ samāsādya vividhāyudhapāṇayaḥ|
rākṣasābhidravantyeva vairiṇo vairiṇaṃ yathā|| 38.12||
tasmādutthāya vegena vṛkṣaṃ yadyabhirohati|
tatra taiḥ kaṇṭakaistīkṣṇairbhidyate chidyate 'api ca|| 38.13||
patraiśca vividhākārairayastuṇḍaiśca pakṣibhiḥ|
hṛtakarṇākṣināsoṣṭhaḥ patito dharaṇītale|| 38.14||
tatra sūcibhirugrābhiḥ sarvāṅgeṣu vibhidyate|
evaṃ bahuvidhākārā yātanāstatra duḥkhitāḥ|| 38.15||
prāpnivanti durācārā ye tān nigadataḥ śṛṇu|
agnido garadātā ca viyonau yaśca gacchati|| 38.16||
puṃsi yo vocchṛjecchukraṃ viṣado māṃsavikrayī|
samudrayāyī duṣṭātmā yaścaiko miṣṭam aśnute|| 38.17||
atithin nārcayedyaśca yaśca mithyāvratī bhavet|
brahmojjhaśca vivāsāśca yopo rpaviśate dvijaḥ|| 38.18||
ghaṇṭiko grāmayājī ca śūdrādhyāpaka eva ca|
tathā vārdhuṣiko lubdho brahmaṇaścaiva vikrayī|| 38.19||
ete gacchanti durvṛttāḥ kūṭaśālmalisaṃjñakam|
koṭīdvayena tūttirṇā varṣāṇāṃ vai punaśca te|| 38.20||
ucchraye pātitāḥ stokaṃ kālaṃ viśrāmya vai punaḥ|
pātyante narake tasmin yāvat kṣīṇaṃ tadenasam|
eṣaiva vidhiranyeṣāṃ narakāṇāṃ mune smṛtaḥ|| 38.21||
ya imaṃ bṛśaduḥkhitopalambhaṃ sukṛtīnām atidurgamācalam|
śṛṇuyāt prayataḥ kutūhalātmā na sa gacchennirayaṃ hi śālmalam|| 38.22||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane
kūṭaśālmalikarthanaṃ nāma aṣṭatriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 38.38||

ūnacatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi narakaṃ kālasūtrakam|
samantānmahatoccena prākāreṇa susaṃvṛtam|| 39.1||
lohajālena ca tathā ākāśe 'apyabhisaṃvṛtaḥ|
yathaikaśca tathā sarve narakā abhisaṃvṛtāḥ|| 39.2||
socchrayāścaiva vijñeyā na vakṣye tānahaṃ punaḥ|
lokadruho janāstatra yātyante puruṣādhamāḥ|| 39.3||
ye haranti striyaṃ vāpi vikretā yastathā gavām|
dharmasya cātmanaścaiva brāhmaṇānāṃ ca nindakaḥ|| 39.4||
chadmanā yaśca śāstrāṇi gurubho 'apahnavet punaḥ|
guruṃ nindati yaścāpi pitaraṃ mātaraṃ tathā|| 39.5||
śvaśuraṃ bhrātaraṃ jyeṣṭhaṃ tathā cānyān garīyasaḥ|
ākrośayati yastān vai tathā cāpyavamanyate|| 39.6||
āśramāṇāṃ tathā bhettā rahasyānāṃ ca sarvaśaḥ|
adattaṃ yaḥ samādadyāt sa gaccheddvija tatra vai|| 39.7||
te tatra patitā ghore narake pāpcetasaḥ|
tisraḥ koṭīstu saṃpūrṇā varṣāṇāṃ tu narādhamāḥ|
yātyante mṛtyuvacanāt krandamānā vicetasaḥ|| 39.8||
kālasūtreṇa mahatā mitvā mitvā tu duṣkṛtam|
chindantyaṅgāni jantūnāṃ kuṇṭhāgrairāyudhairbhṛśam|| 39.9||
kiṃkaraistairaviśrāntaṃ divārātram atandritaiḥ|
pūrṇe kāle tato janturucchrayān pratipadyate|| 39.10||
viśrāmya sa tadā jantuḥ pātyate narake punaḥ|
yāvadasya kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ kṣīṇaṃ sarvam aśeṣataḥ|| 39.11||
ya imaṃ bahupāpakartṛsūtraṃ śṛṇuyādduṣkaralokakarmasūtram|
na sa yāti tadugraduḥkhasūtraṃ narakaṃ tadyamalokakālasūtram|| 39.12||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane kālasūtraṃ nāma
ūnacatvāriśattamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 39.39||

catvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi kumbhīpākaṃ mahābhayam|
śrotR̥ṇām api tatkālaṃ bhayadaṃ hyakṛtātmanām|| 40.1||
āyasyastatra bahvyaśca añjanācalasannibhāḥ|
kumbhyastailena sampūrṇā vahnivarṇāḥ suduḥsahāḥ|| 40.2||
duṣkṛtīṃstāsu taptāsu baddhvā baddhvā mahābalāḥ|
kṣipanti rākṣasā ghorāḥ krandamānāḥ subhairavam|| 40.3||
varṣakoṭīścatasraśca pacyante tatra jantavaḥ|
ye tānimān nibodha tvam ucyamānān mayā vibho|| 40.4||
iṣṭakāpākakārīca kumbhapākakarastathā|
tau vināśayate yaśca agnido yo gṛheṣu ca|| 40.5||
vane khale 'atha goṣṭhe vā annapānavināśakaḥ|
bhojane vighnakārī ca yajñahā yajñadāhakaḥ|| 40.6||
kūṭakarmakaro yaśca kūṭasākṣī tathaiva ca|
mithyāgnicayanī caiva mithyāgnyāharaṇī tathā|| 40.7||
mithyāpākapradātā ca edānāṃ yaśca dūṣakaḥ|
hartopakaraṇānāṃ ca śilpināṃ yo narādhamaḥ|| 40.8||
evaṃ te yātitāstatra viśrāmaṃ punarucchraye|
samprāpya narake bhūyo nipatanti kṣayāntikam|| 40.9||
ya imaṃ bahuduṣkṛtāntapākaṃ śṛṇuyādvā manujo hi karmapākam|
na sa gacchati taṃ durātmapākaṃ narakaṃ sādhanaduḥkhakumbhapākam|| 40.10||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane kumbhīpāko nāma
catvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 40.40||

ekacatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi asipatravanaṃ punaḥ|
narakaṃ pāpakṛdduḥkhaṃ sarvasatvabhayaṃkaram|| 41.1||
asipatra iti khyātā vṛkṣāstatra durāsadāḥ|
bahavaḥ sumahāśākhā ghanāścoccāśca te bhṛśam|| 41.2||
teṣāṃ patrāṇi ghorāṇi tīkṣṇānyasinibhāni ca|
āyasebhyo viśiṣṭāni na ca tāni āyasāni hi|| 41.3||
taikṣṇyāt tāni viśiṣṭāni chedane ca mahāmate|
taiḥ patrairācitāścaiva tathā kaṇṭakinaśca te|| 41.4||
jantavastatra rakṣobhiḥ pāpakarmanibandhanāḥ|
vadhyamānāsimuśalaistathaivānyairmahāyudhaiḥ|| 41.5||
agninā dahyamānāśca vṛkṣāṃstān samprayānti te|
tān āgatān samīkṣyaiva parṇāni prapatantyuta|| 41.6||
mahāgurūṇi tīkṣṇāni vinikṛntanti tāṃśca ha|
te nikṛttaśirogrīvā deśāt tasmāt prayānti vai|| 41.7||
te gatā rākṣasairbhūyo bhūyo vṛkṣairdurāsadaiḥ|
yātyante varṣakoṭīstu tatra pañca suduḥkhitāḥ|| 41.8||
tato vimuktāstebhyaste ucchrayān saṃviśanti hi|
viśrāntāstatra te sarve ucchrayānnarake punaḥ|| 41.9||
pātyante vivaśā mūḍhā yāvat pāpaṃ kṣayaṃ gatam|
ye tu taṃ narakaṃ ghoraṃ narā gacchanti pāpinaḥ|| 41.10||
tāṃste 'ahaṃ sampravakṣyāmi śṛṇuṣvāvahito dvija|
vṛkṣaṃ yaḥ putrakṛtakaṃ vināśayati durmatiḥ|| 41.11||
ārāme vātha grāme vā vikrīṇāti ca durmatiḥ|
niṣpāditaṃ tathā vṛkṣam āśrame pathi vā punaḥ|| 41.12||
taḍāge vā tathodyāne devatāyataneṣu vā|
gṛhe prapāyām atha vā nadyāstīre catuṣpathe|| 41.13||
yatra vā tatra vā jātaṃ yo nāśayati durmatiḥ|
pādapān gulmavallīrvā kṣupānatha tṛṇānyapi|| 41.14||
chāyāpuṣpaphalārthaṃ hi svakāryakaraṇāya vā|
vināśayati yo mūḍhaḥ sa ca taṃ pratipadyate|| 41.15||
yaścāpaharate mūlaṃ puṣpāṇi ca phalāni ca|
ātmārthaṃ kāmasampattau na devapitṛkāraṇāt|| 41.16||
nadīṃ yaścāvarudhnīyāt kūpān yaśca prapūrayet|
yaśca parṇatvacām arthe vṛkṣaṃ chindyānnarādhamaḥ|
vināśayedvā taṃ vṛkṣaṃ sa ca taṃ pratipadyate|| 41.17||
yaśca chāyāsamāsannāñjantūn vai samprabādhate|
svasthānaṃ ca samāsannāṃstrāsayedvārayedapi|| 41.18||
sarve te taṃ prapadyante socchrayaṃ narakaṃ mahat|
uttīrṇāśca tato bhūyaḥ saṃsāraṃ yānti te śubhāḥ|| 41.19||
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyādatandritātmā narakaṃ pāpakṛtām aśarmabhūtam|
na a taṃ samupaiti puṇyakarmā viditātmā hyasipatranāmadheyam|| 41.20||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane
asipatravanaṃ nāma ekacatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 41.41||

dvicatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
ataḥ paraṃ vaitaraṇīṃ nadīṃ pāpapraṇāśanīm|
śṛṇuṣvāvahitaḥ putra pāpakarmabhayāvahām|| 42.1||
nadī vaitaraṇī putra ṭaṅkacchinnataṭā śubhā|
keśāsthirudhirāpūrṇā mahākṣārarasā tathā|| 42.2||
ullumpakairgardabhakairmakaraiḥ kacchapairapi|
śiśumāraiśca nakraiśca tantukai rākṣasairapi|| 42.3||
mahādaṃṣṭrairmahākāyaiḥ piśitāśaiḥ samākulā|
asipatraiśca tairvṛkṣaistīrajātaiḥ samāvṛtā|| 42.4||
śaivalena ca dīrgheṇa vitāneneva saṃvṛtā|
tasyāstīre vanaṃ ghoraṃ śarabharkṣasamākulam|| 42.5||
vyāghradvīpisamākīrṇaṃ siṃhebhakharasaṃkulam|
tatra duṣkṛtakarmāṇastairvyāghrādibhirarditāḥ|| 42.6||
tāṃ nadīṃ sumahāghorāṃ pātyante duḥkhitāstataḥ|
tatra te patitā vatsa tantukaiḥ śaivalena ca|| 42.7||
vitānena ca saṃnaddhā bhakṣyante tairjhaṣādibhiḥ|
kṣārodakena dahyanto nādayantaśca duḥkhitāḥ|| 42.8||
ṣaḍvarṣakoṭīryātyante yāvat pāpasya saṃkṣayaḥ|
tato muktāstūcchrayeṣu pātyante vai punaḥ punaḥ|| 42.9||
viśrāntāstatra te sarve ucchrayānnarake punaḥ|
pātyante vivaśā mūḍhā yāvat pāpaṃ kṣayaṃ gatam|| 42.10||
uttīrṇaḥ socchrayānetān saṃsāraṃ pratipadyate|
tīrṇo 'antameṣu ca punarnarakeṣu pṛthak pṛthak|
koṭirekā tu kālasya vardhate hyuttarottaram|| 42.11||
ucchrayāṇāṃ tu sarveṣām ekaikasya pṛthak pṛthak|
sahasraṃ vardhate putra varṣāṇāṃ vai samāsataḥ|| 42.12||
ye tu gacchanti taṃ ghoraṃ narakaṃ duṣṭacetasaḥ|
śṛṇuṣva tānimān samyagucyamānān mayānagha|| 42.13||
saritaṃ yo 'abhiśapate yaścainām avamanyate|
yaśca nagnaḥ praviśati striyaṃ yaścātra gacchati|| 42.14||
niṣṭhīvedatha mūtraṃ vā purīṣaṃ vāpyathotsṛjet|
apaśca harate yastu kṣetrārāmajanopagāḥ|| 42.15||
apāṃ setuharaścaiva taḍāgasya ca bhedakaḥ|
tathā puṣkariṇīnāṃ ca dūṣako yaśca mānavaḥ|| 42.16||
duṣṭām aduṣṭām atha vā yaśca nārīṃ pradūṣayet|
padminīṃ yaśca harati nāśayedvāpi durmatiḥ|| 42.17||
sārthasya vātha jantorvā yo janturbhayam āvahet|
te sarve narakaṃ ghoraṃ prapadyante narādhamāḥ|| 42.18||
ya imām aśubhapraṇāśinīṃ śṛṇuyānnityam aśuddhavādhanīm|
prayataḥ sa na yāti bhāvanīṃ saritaṃ vaitaraṇīm asaṅginīm|| 42.19||
it skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane vaitaraṇīnāma
dvicatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 42.42||

tricatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi narakaṃ pāpanāśanam|
ayodhanam iti khyātaṃ sarvaprāṇibhayaṃkaram|| 43.1||
yatra te puruṣā ghorā yamābhā yamakiṃkarāḥ|
mahābalā mahāsattvāḥ sarve yogeśvarāstathā|| 43.2||
ayaskārā yathā piṇḍam ayaso 'agnipratāpitam|
saṃdeśenābhisaṃgṛhya sthāpayitvāyase ghane|| 43.3||
abhighnanti ghanairanyaistathā tatrāpi jantavaḥ|
hanyante rākṣasairghoraistarjayadbhiḥ sudāruṇam|| 43.4||
varṣakoṭīstathā sapta yātitāḥ svena karmaṇā|
ucchrayeṣu tathā ghorāṃ yātanāṃ prāpnuvanti te|| 43.5||
etadye yānti puruṣāḥ socchrayaṃ narakaṃ mahat|
tānahaṃ sampravakṣyāmi anirdeśyān narādhamān|| 43.6||
pādena hanyāt pitaraṃ mātaraṃ pūjyam eva vā|
anyāṃ kāṃcit striyaṃ vāpi hastenātha kaśādibhiḥ|| 43.7||
tathā pravajitaṃ caiva agniṃ vāpyatha laṅghayet|
bālam arthakṛte yaśca mṛtyunā yojayet tathā|| 43.8||
striyaṃ vātha pumāṃsaṃ vā klībaṃ vānyaṃ narādhamaḥ|
bhrātR̥n yaścābhisandhatte dravye kasmiṃścideva hi|| 43.9||
pitaraṃ vāpi durbuddhirmātaraṃ bhaginīm api|
patiryaścaiva bhāryāṃ svāṃ putrāṃścaivābhisaṃdhayet|
bhāryā patiṃ vā putrān vā teṣāṃ sā gatirucyate|| 43.10||
kīlayedyaśca devārcāstīrthāni ca durātmavān|
vidyāḥ śāstrāṇi divyāni teṣāṃ sā gatirucyate|| 43.11||
ya imaṃ bahupāpayogakāraṇaṃ śṛṇuyānnityam asaukhyasarvadāraṇam|
prayataḥ sa na yāti taṃ bhayānakaṃ narakaṃ durgamayodhanāvatānakam|| 43.12||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane ayodhanaṃ nāma
tricatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 43.43||

catuścatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
ataḥ paraṃ padmam ahaṃ pravakṣyāmi sudurgamam|
sukṛtīnām alabhyaṃ ca duṣkṛtīnāṃ bhayāvaham|| 44.1||
tatrāgnistāpano nāma dhamyamāna iva jvalan|
jantavastatra tāpyante vahnivarṇā bhavanti ca|| 44.2||
padmapatranibhāḥ sarve dhāmyamānāstatastataḥ|
tasya madhye mahāstambho lauhaḥ samavatiṣṭhate|| 44.3||
taṃ te gatvā pragūhanti so 'apyagniratidāruṇaḥ|
evaṃ tatrāniśaṃ ghoraṃ yātitāstūcchrayeṣvapi|| 44.4||
narāstaṃ yānti niḥsaṅgaṃ ye tān me tvaṃ niśāmaya|
gurubhāryāṃ ca yo gacchedgurusvaṃ vā hareta yaḥ|| 44.5||
devadravyaṃ bhakṣayedyo nāśayedvāpyabhīkṣṇaśaḥ|
brāhmaṇasvaṃ haredyaśca balāddhārayate 'api vā|| 44.6||
bāladravyāpahārī ca hartā ca strīdhanasya ca|
klīvāṃśca tyajate yaśca yo hanyāccharaṇāgatam|| 44.7||
dhanaṃ cāsyābhimanyeta devadravyaharaśca yaḥ|
sarvabhakṣa yaḥ syādvai yaśca pānīyavikrayī|| 44.8||
somavikrayikaścaiva agnyutsādaka eva ca|
agnipraharaṇo yaśca viṣapraharaṇaśca yaḥ|| 44.9||
aśastraṃ yaśca saṃgrāme hanyācchatreṇa mānavaḥ|
yācamānaṃ tathā caiva upaviṣṭam athāpi vā|| 44.10||
parāṅmukhaṃ ca saṃsaktam anyena saha vādinam|
ete sarve narāstatra gacchantyakṛtabuddhayaḥ|| 44.11||
ya idaṃ śṛṇuyāt kṛtāntasadma prayato nityam anekaduḥkhasadma|
sa na yāti tam ugraśokapadmaṃ narakaṃ mṛtyum ivātikālasadma|| 44.12||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane padmo nāma
catuścatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 44.44||

pañcacatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
mahāpadmastataścānyo nirayo romaharṣaṇaḥ|
yatra te kiṃkarā ghorā yamasya yamasaṃnibhāḥ|| 45.1||
jantūnām āyudhaiḥ kuṇṭhairnighṛṇāḥ pāpakarmiṇām|
utkṛtyotkṛtya māṃsāni tebhyo yacchanti vai punaḥ|| 45.2||
te bhakṣayitvā māṃsāni svāni duṣkṛtakāriṇaḥ|
padmapatranibhā jātā dhāmyante 'agnau divāniśam|| 45.3||
analena ca ghoreṇa dravīkṛtam ayaḥ punaḥ|
mukhe 'apāvṛtya yacchanti dāruṇā yamakiṃkarāḥ|| 45.4||
ayomayāstathā nāryo narāścāgnisamaprabhāḥ|
samāśliṣyanti saṃgatya dravamāṇāstatastataḥ|| 45.5||
vṛkṣāśca bahavastatra supuṣyāḥ phalapatriṇaḥ|
tān āśrayanti duḥkhārtā agniṃ varṣanti te 'api ca|| 45.6||
śilāśca bahvyastatrānyāstāḥ śliṣyanti yadā ca te|
tadā tāścāgnivarṇābhā dahante tān bhṛśaṃ narān|| 45.7||
evam eṣa mahāpadmo narakaḥ samprakīrtitaḥ|
suvarṇahārī yaścaiva mātṛyāyī ca yo naraḥ|| 45.8||
mātā putraṃ ca yo 'abhyeti vedadūṣyavakīrṇakaḥ|
matsarī yaśca durvṛttaḥ śramaṇānāṃ ca pūjakaḥ|| 45.9||
vṛṣalo yaḥ śrutiṃ brūyācchṛṇuyādapi vā punaḥ|
gṛhṇīyādvāpi durbuddhirbrāhmaṇān vāvamanyate|| 45.10||
brāhmaṇebhyo rahasyāni āśramāntarajāni ca|
yasminnadhikṛto na syācchṛṇuyādvā paṭheta vā|| 45.11||
duṣṭaśramaṇanirgranthā tathaivājīvakāśca ye|
bhaktastebhyo dvijo yaśca narakaṃ sa prapadyate|| 45.12||
yogaṃ parivadedyaśca pitR̥nnatha pitāmahān|
yogeśvarāṃśca durvṛtto yogadharmam athāpi vā|| 45.13||
vedavarṇāśramā yajñāstannindābhirataḥ śaṭaḥ|
nāstiko hetuvādī ca sarvastaṃ pratipadyate|
tathyam uktaṃ mayā sarvam evam etanna saṃśayaḥ|| 45.14||
evaṃ te yātitāstatra svakarmaphalabandhanāḥ|
tataḥ śeṣeṇa sambaddhā jāyante kīṭayoniṣu|| 45.15||
śṛṇuyādya imaṃ vicintya dhīmān matimān nityam alobhamohaśokaḥ|
sa tu daivavidhipracoditātmā divam evaiti na yāti taṃ kadācit|| 45.16||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane mahāpadmo nāma
pañcacatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 45.45||

ṣaṭcatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi rauravaṃ narakaṃ punaḥ|
yatra te vivaśā baddhāḥ karmaṇā svena jantavaḥ|| 46.1||
yātyante duḥkhaśokārttā mahānirayagāminaḥ|
ru iti procyate śabdastatrāsau śrūyate yataḥ|| 46.2||
punaḥ punarvā bhīmo hi rauravastena kathyate|
pūrṇastu sarvaḥ kārīṣyājjvalate so 'atidāruṇaḥ|| 46.3||
madhye stambho 'asya lauho vai taptakāñcanasaprabhaḥ|
tatra janturbṛśaṃ magnaḥ praviśan dahyate 'avaśaḥ|| 46.4||
ārtanādān prakurvāṇo mūrchitaḥ patitaḥ punaḥ|
tataḥ kleśena mahatā uddhṛtyātmānam ātmanā|| 46.5||
bhūyo 'anyaṃ deśam āsādya tathaiva praviśecca saḥ|
tatastasmādupotpatya stambham āśrayate yadi|| 46.6||
tenāpi dahyate bhūyo visṛjya praviśet punaḥ|
evaṃ sa yātyate tatra bahūnabdān suduḥkhitaḥ|| 46.7||
tato visṛṣṭo bhūyaśca ucchrayān pratipadyate|
taṃ hi gacchanti puruṣāḥ surāpā dharmadeśakāḥ|| 46.8||
pitṛhā mātṛhā caiva bhrātṛhā guruhā tathā|
-- -- -- vādebhiratāsteṣām eva ca nindakāḥ|| 46.9||
goghno 'atha damakaścaiva jantūnāṃ bhṛśadāruṇaḥ|
galakartā kūṭamānī karmaṇānukaroti yaḥ|| 46.10||
parivittiḥ parivettā śmaśānaratireva ca|
punarbhūsutasaṃyogī yasyā copapatirgṛhe|
ete sarve 'abhigacchanti narakaṃ rauravaṃ narāḥ|| 46.11||
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyācca rauravaṃ narakaṃ pāpakṛtāṃ surauravam|
niyataṃ prayato 'atirauravaṃ na sa gacchenmanasāpi rauravam|| 46.12||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane rauravaṃ nāma
ṣaṭcatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 46.46||

saptacatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
mahārauravam anyacca śṛṇu me duṣṭayātanam|
yatra dhārāśca toyaṃ ca taḍāgāni ca putraka|| 47.1||
kārīṣī kanakābhāśca kulyāścāgniprapūritāḥ|
āyasā bahavaḥ stambhā vṛkṣāśca bahukaṇṭakāḥ|| 47.2||
rākṣasā vividhākārāstīkṣṇaśastrāstradhāriṇaḥ|
tatra pāpena bahunā jantuḥ samabhipāśitaḥ|| 47.3||
nipatedvikṛtākāraḥ krandamāno muhurmuhuḥ|
sa tatra patitaḥ kṣipraṃ rākṣasairbhinnamastakaḥ|| 47.4||
kārīṣyām agnivarṇāyāṃ pacyate bhṛśadāruṇam|
tataḥ sa tena dāhena duḥkhitaḥ paramārtimān|| 47.5||
dāhapraśamanārthāya taḍāge vinimajjati|
tatra kṣāreṇa taptena dviguṇaṃ vedanārditaḥ|| 47.6||
vegenotthāya vṛkṣaṃ vā stambhaṃ vāpyadhirohati|
tatra taiḥ kaṇṭakaistīkṣṇairāyasaiścāvatakṣitaḥ|| 47.7||
patate hyagnikulyāyāṃ karuṇaṃ bahudhā nadan|
evaṃ sa yātyamānastu tṛṣārtto vilapan bahu|| 47.8||
dhārām āśrayate pātuṃ sāpi tasyāyasaṃ tadā|
agnivarṇaṃ vahatyambhastato mūrcchārdito mriyet|| 47.9||
sampūrṇayātanaścāpi muktastasmānmahābhayāt|
ucchrayeṣu tadā janturyātyate bhṛśadāruṇam|| 47.10||
tatra gacchati rājaghno rājabhāryāvamānakaḥ|
āśāṃ dattvā na dadyādyo yaśca tīrthāvadūṣakaḥ|| 47.11||
moṣakaḥ sūcakaścaiva strībhṛto yaśca pāpakṛt|
agnau gavi ca yo dānaṃ brāhmaṇe cāpi vārayet|| 47.12||
vikrīṇīyāt svabhāryāṃ yo hyapatyaṃ vā narādhamaḥ|
harate cāgnibhaṇḍāni yogināṃ caiva kiṃcana|| 47.13||
corān vā yo 'anugṛhṇāti manuṣyāstasya ye ca ha|
brāhmaṇādhikṛtaścaiva dharmādhikṛta eva ca|| 47.14||
kapilā yasya gauḥ syācca anagnerbrāhmaṇasya ha|
mithyāgnihotrī yaścaiva naityake pariveṣakaḥ|| 47.15||
rājaputravadhaṃ caiva durbhikṣaṃ yacca cintayet|
rāṣṭralopaṃ dāralopaṃ dhanalopaṃ ca yo naraḥ|| 47.16||
deśavidra${\rm (}A{\rm )}$vaṇaṃ caiva yaḥ kuryāḍḍāmarāṇi vā|
sarve te narakaṃ yānti mahārauravasaṃjñakam|| 47.17||
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyādabhīkṣṇaśo niyataṃ dharmamatiśca tiṣṭhati|
na sa gacchati taṃ bhayāvahaṃ narakaṃ rauravam ugrarauravam|| 47.18||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane mahārauravaṃ nāma
saptacatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 47.44||

aṣṭacatvāriṃśo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
tamo nāmāparo ghoro narako 'atibhayaṃkaraḥ|
tatra so 'abhipatanneva rākṣasairabhihanyate|| 48.1||
asimudgaraśaṅkvagrairgadāmuśalapaṭṭiśaiḥ|
bhayadaiḥ parighaiḥ ṭaṅkairvajrairṛṣṭiparaśvadhaiḥ|| 48.2||
anyaiśca vividhākārairhataḥ kruddhaiḥ sunirdayaiḥ|
mūrchitastamasā grasto narakaṃ taṃ prapadyate|| 48.3||
sa dehena vinaṣṭena tamasā mūrcchitākṛtiḥ|
suḥkhasantatisaṃnaddho yātanām aśnute bhṛśam|| 48.4||
yasmāt sa tamasā grasto 'anāśvasto 'atidāruṇām|
yātanām aśnute jantustamastasmāt sa ucyate|| 48.5||
sarvā bahuvidhākārā yātanā yāḥ prakīrtitāḥ|
tāstatra samavāpnoti svena pāpena durmatiḥ|| 48.6||
samāptayātanaścāpi santīrṇasvena karmaṇā|
ucchrayeṣu punarjanturyātyate karmabandhanaḥ|| 48.7||
brahmahā bhrūṇahā caiva surāpo brāhmaṇaśca yaḥ|
gavāṃ nipāne yaścaiva pipāsūnāṃ narādhamaḥ|| 48.8||
vighnaṃ karoti mohāndha āhūya bhartsayet tu yaḥ|
brāhmaṇān dveṣṭi nityaṃ yo 'arthinaṃ yaśca dūṣayet|| 48.9||
śāstrāṇi harate yaśca goghno yaśca naraḥ smṛtaḥ|
kāpilaśca vṛthādṛṣṭirvedadharmārthadūṣakaḥ|| 48.10||
brāhmaṇākrośakaścaiva vedadharmārthadūṣakaḥ|
nāstikāśca surātmāna ityete taṃ prayānti vai|| 48.11||
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyāt tamomayaṃ tamasā nityam atandritendriyaḥ|
na sa yāti tamomayaṃ sadā narakaṃ dāruṇajantuśokadam|| 48.12||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane
tamo nāma aṣṭacatvāriṃśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 48.41||

ūnapañcāśattamo .adhyāyaḥ|
suśarmovāca|
tamastamataraṃ ghoraṃ narakaṃ śṛṇvataḥ param|
prakāśo yatra naivāsti naiva dṛṣṭiḥ pravartate|| 49.1||
patanneva narastatra visaṃjñaḥ kriyate tadā|
rākṣasairvikṛtākāraistamastena sa cocyate|| 49.2||
tatrāsau patito mūḍho vahninā dahyate bhṛśam|
tato 'api vegādutthāya dṛṣṭihīno vicetanaḥ|| 49.3||
chidyate bhidyate caiva rākṣasaiḥ krūrakarmabhiḥ|
tasmādapi tathaivārtaḥ so 'anyaṃ deśaṃ prapadyate|| 49.4||
tatrāpi nigṛhītastaiḥ paśumāreṇa māryate|
tato bhūyaśca kūpeṣu kṣipto durgeṣvacetanaḥ|| 49.5||
nimagnaścāgnikārīṣyāṃ niṣkūjan so 'abhijāyate|
evaṃ sa yātanā bahvīstvanubhūya suduḥkhitaḥ|| 49.6||
narakāntam anuprāpya ucchrayeṣvabhipātyate|
garbhapātanakāraśca rājyakāmaśca yo bhavet|| 49.7||
ihaivānarhamāno 'asau (?) bhṛtyo rājavadhe rataḥ|
anācāryaśca yaḥ karma ācāryāṇāṃ prapadyate|| 49.8||
śāstravidyauṣadhīnāṃ ca gadānām agadaiḥ saha|
yo vināśayitā kaścidyaḥ praśaṃsati dānavān|| 49.9||
upadeśaṃ ca yo dveṣādācāryo na prayacchati|
sa yāti narakaṃ ghoraṃ dustaraṃ taṃ tamomayam|| 49.10||
kṛtaghnaṃ tu samāsādhya nārakāḥ sarva eva te|
yamaṃ praṇamya bruvate saha tairyamakiṃkaraiḥ|| 49.11||
bhagavan na vayaṃ śaktāḥ pāpasyāsya vināśane|
upāyam anyaṃ paśyeha prasādaṃ kuru naḥ prabho|| 49.12||
sa evam ukto bhagavān yamaḥ pretādhipastadā|
sarvadharmārthakuśalān pṛcchati smarṣisattamān|| 49.13||
bhagavantaḥ kathaṃ tvasya kṛtaghnasya durātmanaḥ|
niṣkṛtiḥ sumahāghorādbhavet pāpasya karmaṇaḥ|| 49.14||
tataste ṛṣayaḥ sarve dṛṣṭvā dīrgheṇa cakṣuṣā|
yamaṃ dharmabhṛtāṃ śreṣṭham idaṃ vai bruvate vacaḥ|| 49.15||
brahmaghne ca surāpe ca core bhagnavrate tathā|
niṣkṛtirvihitā sadbhiḥ kṛtaghne nāsti niṣkṛtiḥ|| 49.16||
tataḥ sa bhagavān devo mārtaṇḍatanayo varaḥ|
nārakebhyo dadāti ājñāṃ sarve yūyam imaṃ naram|| 49.17||
śodhayiṣyatha gacchadhvaṃ naikā hyasya gatiḥ smṛtā|
tataste tasya vacanānnārakāḥ pāpakarmiṇam|| 49.18||
sarveṣvevānupūrvyeṇa yātayantyatidāruṇāḥ|
bhartṛpiṇḍāpahartā ca pitṛpiṇḍāpahārakaḥ|| 49.19||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
tasmādgṛhītvā vidyāṃ ca dakṣiṇāṃ yo na yacchati|| 49.20||
puṣṭaśca yastaṃ nānveti yaśca taṃ ghātayennaraḥ|
kṛtasya doṣaṃ vadati sakāmaṃ na karoti ca|| 49.21||
na smarecca kṛtaṃ yastu āśramān yaśca dūṣayet|
na puṣṇāti tathā vāhān āśritāṃścopakāriṇaḥ|| 49.22||
bhṛtyāṃśca karmaniratāṃstathaiva hitakāriṇaḥ|
bhāryāṃ karmakarāṇāṃ ca narmāṇi vadate ca yaḥ|| 49.23||
na dattaṃ na hutaṃ kiṃcidamuṣminniti yo vadet|
sarvāṃstānṛṣibhiḥ sārdhaṃ kṛtaghnānabravīnmanuḥ|| 49.24||
kṛtaghnaśca śaṭhaścaiva nāstikocchinnasaṃśayaḥ|
etān sarve 'abhigacchanti ya ete kīrtitā mayā|| 49.25||
janetā copanetā ca yaśca vidyāṃ prayacchati|
bhayatrātānnadātā ca pañcaite pitaraḥ smṛtāḥ|| 49.26||
yasteṣāṃ doṣavaktā ca abhyasūyaka eva ca|
tathā drohapravṛttaśca santyajet tān narādhamān|| 49.27||
mitradhugyaśca duṣṭātmā tasya randhrāvakīrtitaḥ|
kṛtopakāriṇe purrvaṃ na karoti priyaṃ ca yaḥ|| 49.28||
ete sarve narā duṣṭāḥ sarva evāśubhe ratāḥ|
narakān samprapadyante baddhāḥ pāpena karmaṇā|| 49.29||
ete sarve mayā proktā mahānirayagāminaḥ|
ucchrayāneva gacchanti ye 'anye pāpakṛto narāḥ|| 49.30||
ya imaṃ tāmasaṃ ghoraṃ śṛṇuyādvā paṭheta vā|
adharmaśca nivarteta sa gacchedbrahmaṇaḥ padam|| 49.31||
iti skandapurāṇe narakavarṇane tamo 'atitamaṃ nāma
ūnapañcāśattamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 49.39||

pañcāśo .adhyāyaḥ|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi saṃsāraparivartanam|
yathā vai narakāt tīrṇaḥ saṃsaranti samāsataḥ|| 50.1||
prathame narake proktā ye mayā āpakarmiṇaḥ|
śeṣeṇa karmaṇā te tu jāyante kṛmiyoniṣu|| 50.2||
kṛmiyonau parāvṛttāḥ sahasrāṇāṃ śataṃ samāḥ|
tataḥ punarmarkaṭāste jāyante 'atha tarakṣavaḥ|| 50.3||
tatra tāvat parāvṛttā jāyante goṣu te yadā|
tadā tatra śatenaiva janmanāṃ śeṣatastataḥ|| 50.4||
mānuṣeṣūpajāyante tāvadeva na saṃśayaḥ|
tatra te kurvate bhūyo yadi kiṃcinna kilbiṣam|| 50.5||
tato viśuddhāṃ jātiṃ te labhante punareva tu|
na ca bhūyo 'api te ghoraṃ saṃsāraṃ prāpnuvanti vai|| 50.6||
dvitīye tu mayā proktāste muktāḥ śeṣakarmaṇā|
kṛmikīṭeṣu jāyante sahasrāṇāṃ śatāni ṣaṭ|| 50.7||
tathā śatasahasraṃ ca śatānāṃ te punargatāḥ|
matsyayonau prasūyante tāvadeva na saṃśayaḥ|| 50.8||
tato vyāghrāśca ṛkṣāśca tato gotvam avāpyate|
mānuṣeṣūpapadyante kutsitāḥ svena karmaṇā|| 50.9||
tṛtīye tvatha ye proktā mayā duṣkṛtakāriṇaḥ|
te muktāḥ karmaṇastasmāccheṣeṇa samaveṣṭitāḥ|| 50.10||
kṛmikīṭeṣu jāyante sahasrāṇāṃ śatāni ṣaṭ|
tathaivadaśa cānyāni pakṣiṇastāvadeva ca|| 50.11||
tataḥ siṃhāśca sarpāśca gāvaḥ paścācca mānuṣāḥ|
caturthe tvatha ye proktā mayā duṣkṛtakāriṇaḥ|| 50.12||
te sarve śeṣavantastu jāyante kṛmiyoniṣu|
sahasrāṇāṃ śatānyaṣṭau tathā cānyāni ṣoḍaśa|| 50.13||
yonīnāṃ hi tathā bhūyo jāyante te tato mṛgāḥ|
mṛgabhāvādvinirmuktā jāyante ca punaḥ kharāḥ|| 50.14||
tato 'ajā gavayāścāpi gāvo mānuṣatāṃ tataḥ|
pañcame ye mayā proktāste 'api śeṣeṇa karmaṇā|| 50.15||
kṛmikīṭeṣu jāyante janmanāṃ koṭim eva hi|
hastiyonau ca tāvaddhi uṣṭreṣvaśveṣu caiva hi|| 50.16||
tato gotvaṃ samāsādya mānuṣyaṃ prāpnuvanti te|
ṣaṣṭhāccaiva vinirmuktāstataḥ śeṣeṇa karmaṇā|| 50.17||
jāyante kṛmikīṭeṣu janmanāṃ dviguṇena hi|
koṭim ekāṃ tato yūkāstato matsyo 'atha sūkaraḥ|| 50.18||
mahiṣatvaṃ tataḥ prāpya gotvājjāyeta mānuṣaḥ|
mānuṣatve kutsitaśca vyādhitaścaiva jāyate|| 50.19||
saptamācca vinirmuktaḥ kṛmikīṭeṣu jāyate|
koṭītrayaṃ tāvadeva vṛkṣatvam adhigacchati|| 50.20||
tato latā tato gulmastato hastī prajāyate|
gotvaṃ ca samanuprāpya jāyate mānuṣastataḥ|| 50.21||
aṣṭamācca vinirmukto baddhaḥ śeṣeṇa karmaṇā|
jāyate kṛmikīṭeṣu dve koṭyau dviguṇe ca saḥ|| 50.22||
tataścauṣadhibhāvena vīrutsu ca kuśeṣu ca|
tato gotvādvinirmukto jāyate kutsito naraḥ|| 50.23||
navamādapi cottīrṇo baddhaḥ śeṣeṇa karmaṇā|
jāyate kṛmikīṭeṣu pañcakoṭīstataḥ khagaḥ|| 50.24||
tato matsyaśca tāvadvai tāvadeva sarīsṛpaḥ|
śvā tatastāvadevātha tato bhavati kinnaraḥ|| 50.25||
kinnaratvādvinirmuktastato goṣūpajāyate|
tato goyoninirmukto mānuṣeṣūpajāyate|| 50.26||
daśamādapi cottīrṇaḥ ṣaṭ koṭīrjanmanāṃ kṛmiḥ|
śeṣeṇa karmaṇā jātastato bhavati vānaraḥ|| 50.27||
vānarastāvadeveha tāvadeva ca kukkuṭaḥ|
tāvadeva ca kākastu jīvaṃjīvaka eva ca|| 50.28||
vṛkṣadārakamārjārapipilīkāśca jāyate|
tato goṣu prajāto 'asau mānuṣeṣūpajāyate|| 50.29||
mahārauravanirmuktaḥ saptakoṭīḥ suduḥkhitaḥ|
janmanāṃ kṛmikīṭeṣu jāto matsyatvam aśnute|| 50.30||
tataḥ śvā gardabhaścaiva bhaināśī (?) śuka eva ca|
tato bhavati gauścāpi tataḥ ṣaṇḍhaśca mānuṣe|| 50.31||
tamonarakanirmuktastvaṣṭakoṭīḥ suduḥkhitaḥ|
janmanāṃ prāpnute janturviṣṭhāyāṃ kṛmiyoniṣu|| 50.32||
tataḥ śvā jāyate bhūyaścakrāhvaśca punaḥ punaḥ|
tato maṇḍūkatāṃ prāpya jāyate mṛgapakṣiṣu|| 50.33||
jāyate kinnaraścāpi dvīpī śarabha eva ca|
tato gotvaṃ samāsādya mānuṣatvam avāpnute|| 50.34||
tamonarako nirmuktaḥ śeṣeṇaiva hi karmaṇā|
jāyate kṛmikīṭeṣu navakoṭiḥ sa janmanām|| 50.35||
tato bhavati kākaśca bhāsaścaiva tataḥ param|
vāntāśī ca tataḥ pakṣī ulūkaśca tataḥ punaḥ|| 50.36||
punarvṛkṣaśca gulmaśca tato bhavati vai mṛgaḥ|
tato gaurmanujaścāpi garbhasthaḥ sa vipadyate|| 50.37||
punaḥ punarjāyamānaḥ sahasrāṇāṃ śataṃ samāḥ|
vyādhitaḥ kutsitaścaiva jāyate ca punaḥ punaḥ|| 50.38||
yastu sarvānimān prāpya narakāniha jāyate|
sa yoniṣu samastāsu sarvasaṃsāram aśnute|| 50.39||
yadi mānuṣatāṃ yāti kadācit kālaparyayāt|
tatrāpi kutsitāṃ yoniṃ bhūyo bhūyaḥ prapadyate|| 50.40||
aniṣṭaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ duḥkhito vyādhitastathā|
vikṛtaṃ rūpam āpnoti karmaṇā svena duḥkhitaḥ|| 50.41||
devabrāhmaṇavidveṣṭā sarvavratabahiṣkṛtaḥ|
sarvadharmavinirmuktaḥ sādhvācāravivarjitaḥ|| 50.42||
nirnamaskāraduḥśīlaḥ kimbhakṣo brahmanindakaḥ|
na tīrthadevāyatanaḥ svadhāsvastivivarjitaḥ|
akīrtanīyo lokānāṃ jāyate svena karmaṇā|| 50.43||
suśarmovāca|
etat te kathitaṃ sarvaṃ samāsāt putra sarvaśaḥ|
narakāṇāṃ satattvaṃ ca kramabhedo yathāmati|| 50.44||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyādyuktaḥ sadā parvasu parvasu|
śrāvayedvā dvijān samyak sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 50.45||
dhanyaṃ yaśasyam āyuṣyaṃ svargyaṃ sarvārthasādhakam|
śravyaṃ ca paṭhitavyaṃ ca satataṃ bhūtim icchatā|| 50.46||
idaṃ tu sarvārthasukhāvahaṃ dhruvaṃ mahānubhāvaṃ sugatipradaṃ śubham|
sadaiva vipreṇa samāhitātmanā adhītya dhāryaṃ śrutisaṃmitaṃ dhruvam|| 50.47||
iti skandapurāṇe saṃsāragativarṇanaṃ nāma
pañcāśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 50.50||

ekapañcāśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sukeśastu tato vyāsa pituḥ śrutvā sudīnavat|
duḥkhitaścintayāmāsa jantūnāṃ tāṃ gatiṃ tadā|| 51.1||
cintayābhiparītātmā duḥkhena ca samāhataḥ|
jantūnāṃ mokṣaṇopāyaṃ mūḍhacetā na jajñivān|| 51.2||
cintāpannaḥ sa tu yadā pitR̥ṃstān nābhyabhāṣata|
tadā te pitaraḥ sarve sukeśam idam ūcire|| 51.3||
pitara ūcuḥ|
atīva kiṃ cintayasi kutaścintā tavānagha|
īśvarasya sataḥ putra nedaṃ tava vidhīyate|| 51.4||
sukeśa uvāca|
jantūnāṃ karmajaṃ kleśaṃ śrutvā yuṣmābhirīritam|
cintayāmi kathaṃ te.āṃ mokṣopāyo bhavediti|| 51.5||
pitara ūcus|
anādṛtya kṣayaṃ putra mokṣasteṣāṃ na vidyate|
karmaṇaḥ svakṛtasyeha sa ca bhogāt kṣayo mataḥ|| 51.6||
bhogaśca narake 'avaśyaṃ jantūnāṃ saṃvidhīyate|
na ca te nārakāḥ śakyā hartuṃ karmakṣayaṃ vinā|| 51.7||
aśakyāḥ khalu ye hyarthā na tān prājñaḥ samārabhet|
arṇavasya prataraṇaṃ yathā tvāṃ mṛtyum ṛcchati|| 51.8||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktaḥ sa tejasvī pitR̥ṃstān hṛcchayāvṛtaḥ|
uvāca praṇato bhūtvā māvamadhvaṃ sutaṃ hi mām|| 51.9||
kā śaktirmama tāñjantūn balāt tārayituṃ śubhān|
mahādevaprasādastāṃstārayiṣyati durgatīn|| 51.10||
yūyaṃ yathaiva tīrṇāḥ stha narakasthā vicetasaḥ|
tathā te jantavaḥ sarve tariṣyanti na saṃśayaḥ|| 51.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastān sa tadāmantrya mahātmā gaṇanāyakaḥ|
sampraviśya samudrāmbho hyantarjalagatastadā|| 51.12||
jajāpa rudrāñchuddhātmā niścalaḥ susamāhitaḥ|
japatastasya yogena yuktasya ca mahātmanaḥ|| 51.13||
trailokyam akhilaṃ vyāsa tapasābhūt pratāpitam|
tato devāstadā sarve pitāmaham athābruvan|| 51.14||
kim idaṃ bhagavan sarve tapyāma vivaśā vayam|
kasyedaṃ tapaso vīryaṃ kasya yogo 'ayam īdṛśaḥ|| 51.15||
ka eṣa suraśārdūla tapastapyati dāruṇam|
yāvadevaṃ na dahati yāvaccaiva na kupyate|| 51.16||
tāvat sarvānabhiprāyāṃstasya sampādaya prabho|
sa evam ukto devaistairbhagavān devasattamaḥ|| 51.17||
uvāca mā bhayaṃ vo 'astu nāyaṃ kaścidasaṃmataḥ|
sa eṣa devadevasya mahātmā gaṇanāyakaḥ|| 51.18||
samudrāntarjalāsīno rudrāñjapati yogavān|
na cāsya duṣṭo 'abhiprāyo lokān prati mahābalāḥ|| 51.19||
nārakāneṣa narakāduddhartum abhimanyate|
tadyūyaṃ yadi manyadhve gatvā rudraṃ praṇamya ca|| 51.20||
arthayāmo 'asya devasya kriyatām īpsito varaḥ|
evam astviti te sarve brahmaṇā saha saṃgatāḥ|| 51.21||
gatā mandaram avyagrā nandinā sampraveśitāḥ|
te dṛṣṭvā devam īśānaṃ stutvedam abruvan vibhum|| 51.22||
sukeśo bhagavāṃstubhyaṃ vallabho gaṇanāyakaḥ|
kāruṇyaṃ prāṇināṃ kṛtvā tapastapyati duścaram|| 51.23||
tasya kāmaṃ sakāmaṃ tvaṃ kuruṣva bhuvaneśvara|
teṣāṃ vijñaptim ākarṇya devadevastato bhavaḥ|| 51.24||
brahmādyaiḥ sahito 'abhyāgāt sukeśasya tadāntikam|
samudrastatra ye cānye munayaḥ śaṃsitavratāḥ|| 51.25||
ardhyam ādāya śataśas nemuḥ śaṅkaram āgatam|
tam asau gaṇapaśreṣṭhaṃ devadeva idaṃ vacaḥ|| 51.26||
provāca madhuraṃ vyāsa manaḥśrotrasukhāvaham|
vatsottiṣṭha sukeśa tvaṃ prārthayasva yathepsitam|| 51.27||
sarvaṃ tat saṃpradāsyāmi tvaṃ hi nandisamo mama|
tataḥ sukeśa utthāya stutvā ca vṛṣabhadhvajam|| 51.28||
praṇipatya punarvavre kāmaṃ pūrvasamīhitam|
narakeṣu narā deva yātyante pāpakāriṇaḥ|| 51.29||
teṣām upari ceto me duḥkhenārditam īśvara|
te yathā pratimucyante sarva eva jagatprabho|| 51.30||
tathā kuru mamādyaiva vara eṣa mayārhitaḥ|
ye cādhunā narā deva yātyante narakeṣu vai|| 51.31||
teṣāṃ tu pratimokṣārthaṃ yāce 'ahaṃ tvāṃ sureśvara|
tatastadarthitaṃ devaḥ prayacchannidam abravīt|| 51.32||
evaṃ bhavatu te vatsa muktā nārakiṇo narāḥ|
anayāpi ca bhavatyā tvaṃ kāṇruyena ca vallabhaḥ|| 51.33||
sutarāṃ bhava nirvyagraḥ paramaiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|
tataste nārakāḥ sarve vimānāni samāśritāḥ|| 51.34||
devadevaṃ tato 'abhyetya sukeśaṃ ca praṇemire|
tam uvāca punardevaḥ sukeśaṃ gaṇanāyakam|| 51.35||
yo hi tārayate jantūn āpadaḥ kāṃścideva tu|
teṣāṃ dharmapitā bhūtvā saṃsāraṃ na sa paśyati|| 51.36||
manasāpi hi yaḥ prāṇī kleśājjantūn sadecchati|
vimoktuṃ so 'api dharmātmā sarvaduḥkhaiḥ pramucyate|| 51.37||
yaścopārjya svayaṃ dharmaṃ jantubhyaḥ saṃprayacchati|
sukhārthaṃ so 'api sarvebhyo duḥkhebhyaḥ saṃpramucyate|| 51.38||
sa tvaṃ pareṇa yogena aiśvaryeṇa ca saṃyutaḥ|
jantūnāṃ tāraṇe yuktastvayānyaḥ kaḥ samo bhuvi|| 51.39||
sukeśa uvāca|
bhagavaṃstvatprasādānme sarvam etadbhaviṣyati|
śaktirmama kuto deva tvayaivaitat kṛtaṃ prabho|| 51.40||
da cānyadasti kartavyaṃ kṛtyaṃ yanme manogatam|
tavāsmi kiṃkaro dāso nāścaryaṃ yan mamedṛśam|| 51.41||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devo visṛjya gaṇanāyakam|
abhyagānmandaraṃ vyāsa vṛtaḥ sarvāmaraistadā|| 51.42||
devā api vimānasthān nārakān vīkṣya sarvaśaḥ|
śāntaṃ ca jagato duḥkhaṃ dṛṣṭvā jagmuryathāgatam|| 51.43||
ya imaṃ nārakottāraṃ śṛṇuyādvā paṭheta vā|
sa duḥkhaṃ samanuprāpya nāvasīdati karhicit|| 51.44||
etadyogavidhānasarvasamayaṃ śrutvā naro nityaśaḥ pāpātmāpi sunirghṛṇaṃ pratibhayaṃ nābhyeti pāpāśrayam|
kiṃ tvetadya ihābhyupetya satataṃ śaucānvitaḥ śrāvayeddevabrahmaṇavaidyasaṃsadi dṛḍhaṃ bhaktaḥ sadā śaṅkaram|| 51.45||
iti skandapurāṇe nārakīyamokṣaṇe ekapañcāśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 51.51||

dvipañcāśo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
ke punastaṃ na gacchanti narakaṃ śubhakarmiṇaḥ|
pāpeṣvapi ratā brahmannetadicchāmi veditum|| 52.1||
tathā strīṇāṃ ca kā yuktā gatiḥ paramikā śubhā|
kena karmavipākena etadicchāmi veditum|| 52.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
na gacchanti narā yena narakaṃ taṃ suduḥkhitāḥ|
pāpakarmaṇyapi ratāstānimāñchṛṇu mānada|| 52.3||
nāgnicinnarakaṃ yāti na trisūtrī na govratī|
nāśvamedhena yo yaṣṭā gosahasraprado na ca|| 52.4||
na ca svādhyāyanityo yo rudrajāpī ca yo dvijaḥ|
brāhmaṇāṃstārayedyaśca āpado maraṇāntikāt|| 52.5||
brāhmaṇaṃ vyādhitaṃ dīnam anāthaṃ duḥkhapīḍitam|
śuśrūṣedyāvadetena yukto dharmeṇa mānavaḥ|| 52.6||
brāhmaṇaṃ vāsayedyastu gṛhavāsaparicchadaiḥ|
niḥsvaṃ svādhyāyasaṃpannaṃ narakaṃ na sa paśyati|| 52.7||
tathā gāṃ caiva saṃmagnāṃ patitāṃ śaktivarjitām|
saṃrakṣati ca yuktātmā sa ca taṃ naiva gacchati|| 52.8||
maheśaṃ yaśca bhāvena parameṇa samādhinā|
bhaktyā samarcayennityaṃ sa ca taṃ naiva gacchati|| 52.9||
itareṣāṃ tu saṃsāro bhavatyeva na saṃśayaḥ|
brāhmaṇāstaṃ na gacchanti vedavedāṅgapāragāḥ|| 52.10||
ṣaṭkarmaniratā vyāsa ātmadharmavyavasthitāḥ|
tapaḥśaucasamāyuktā dayāvanto dṛḍhavratāḥ|| 52.11||
pratigrahanivṛttāśca īśabhaktāśca ye dvijāḥ|
kṣatriyā ye ca rakṣārthaṃ prajānāṃ nityam udyatāḥ|| 52.12||
tyajanti samare prāṇān na te narakagāminaḥ|
vaiśyā vārtāsamāyuktā nyāyadharmavyavasthitāḥ|| 52.13||
yeṣāṃ vṛttiravicchinnā devabrāhmaṇapūjakāḥ|
narakaṃ te na paśyanti svargagāste prakīrtitāḥ|| 52.14||
bhaktā varṇatrayaṃ ye ca śūdrā darpavivarjitāḥ|
brāhmaṇāṃśca viśeṣeṇa nityaṃ ye samupāsate|| 52.15||
te na paśyanti narakaṃ sugatiṃ ca mṛtā yayuḥ|
caturṣvapi ca varṇeṣu manujā bhāvataḥ śivam|| 52.16||
śarvārpitakriyāvasthā bhaktā nityam anuvratāḥ|
na te prayānti narakaṃ prāpnuvanti parāṃ gatim|| 52.17||
prāsādaṃ caiva ye kṛtvā devadevam upāsate|
anyānapi pitR̥ṃste tu narakāduddharantyuta|| 52.18||
khanitāḥ puṣkariṇyo yaistaḍāgāni hradāni ca|
ropitā vṛkṣaṣaṇḍāśca te 'api tān na prayānti hi|| 52.19||
paritrāṇaṃ dvijātīnām anyeṣāṃ caiva duḥkhinām|
nityaṃ prakurvate ye ca te 'api tān na vrajanti hi|| 52.20||
akrodhanāśca ye nityaṃ devabrāhmaṇapūjakāḥ|
nityaṃ dānaratāścaiva na te gacchantyadhogatim|| 52.21||
satyābhidhānasaṃyuktā dṛṣṭārambhavivarjitāḥ|
svadharmācārasaṃyuktāḥ paśyanti narakaṃ na te|| 52.22||
liṅgārcanaratastasmāt sarvasmāt parimucyate|
dhyānī ta sarvadā yo vai gaṇāñjapati vā śuciḥ|| 52.23||
yogī tu sarsapāpāni kurvannapi na lipyate|
strīṇāṃ tu paramo devaḥ patirbhavati sarvadā|| 52.24||
tasmānnānyaṃ prapaśyanti yāḥ kāściddharmacintikāḥ|
karmaṇā manasā vācā yaddadāti juhoti vā|| 52.25||
parityajya patiṃ nārī na tasya phalam aśnute|
patiśuśrūṣaṇe raktā manovākkāyakarmabhiḥ|| 52.26||
patau mṛte 'api manasā nānyam icchati yā naram|
karoti puṇyaṃ yaccāpi patyuḥ sarvaṃ prayacchati|
sā nārī narakān sarvān manasāpi na gāchati|| 52.27||
saṃsāraṃ naiva sā ghoraṃ sarvaṃ saṃpratipadyate|
anyāsāṃ tu na saṃdeho narakaṃ prati suvrata|| 52.28||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sukeśaṃ tvanugṛhyaivaṃ devo 'api vṛṣavāhanaḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- kāṣṭhakūṭāśramaṃ gataḥ|
anujagrāha taṃ vipraṃ kāṣṭhakūṭaṃ tapodhanam|| 52.29||
vyāsa uvāca|
kiṃ tapastasya bhagavan brāhmaṇasya mahātmanaḥ|
kiyatā caiva kālena varaṃ lebhe maheśvarāt|| 52.30||
kasya putraḥ kasya naptā kinnāmā sa ca sattamaḥ|
etadicchāmi kathitaṃ bhagavan vistarācchubham|| 52.31||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
gautamasyānvaye vipro nāmnā kṛṣṇa iti prabhuḥ|
tasya putro 'abhavat khyāto bhūmanyuriti nāmataḥ|| 52.32||
tasya patnyabhavat sukhrūrātreyī nāmato yaśāḥ|
sa kadācit kṛtodvāho bhūmanyurnāma gautamaḥ|| 52.33||
nāvindata sutaṃ tasyāṃ jarayā cābhisaṃvṛtaḥ|
sa bhāryām āha duḥkhārta idaṃ vacanakovidaḥ|| 52.34||
putreṇecchanti lokāṃśca anṛṇāśca bhavantyuta|
jarāṃ parigataścāhaṃ na ca me dṛśyate sutaḥ|| 35
sā tvaṃ kaṃcit sagotraṃ me anujñātā mayā śubhe|
abhipadyasva putrārthaṃ yāce tvāṃ prāñjalirnataḥ|| 52.36||
suyaśovāca|
na mayā śrutam etat te tathā noktaṃ tvayānagha|
mādṛśī katham etaddhi manasāpyabhicintayet|| 52.37||
atrīṇāṃ tu kule jātā gautamaṃ kulam āgatā|
madvidhā katham etaddhi kuryāt sadbhirvigarhitam|| 52.38||
tapasā dhanam anvicchejjīvitāni sukhāni ca|
putrān kulaṃ ca kolāṃśca tapaḥ kuru mahāmune|| 52.39||
tapasā hi suto labdhaḥ śaktinā sa parāśaraḥ|
aurvaśca tapasā svena cyavanena mahāmuniḥ|| 52.40||
vasiṣṭhena kapiñjalyām indrapramatireva ca|
śilādo 'ajanayaccaiva tapasā nandinaṃ sutam|| 52.41||
tathā bhavānapi tapaḥ karotu susamādhinā|
lapsyase tvaṃ sutaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ mahāyogabalānvitam|| 52.42||
māṃ hi dṛṣṭvā purā prāha atrirbrahmasutaḥ svayam|
satputriṇī bhavitrīyaṃ na mithyā tadbhaviṣyati|| 52.43||
tapo 'asti mayi yat kiṃcit tvatprasādāt samarjitam|
tena svena ca saṃyukto rudram ārādhaya prabho|| 52.44||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktaḥ sa tejasvī hriyā paramayā yutaḥ|
tayaivaṃ samanujñāto rudraṃ śaraṇam īyivān|| 52.45||
tvaritaṃ sa samāgamya narmadāṃ harṣasaṃyutaḥ|
tasyāstīre samudviśya tasthau vāyvāśanaḥ samāḥ|| 52.46||
sa tu naivābhavadvipraḥ kṛtārthastena karmaṇā|
tataḥ sa duḥkhito bhūyaḥ prāṇāyāmena tasthivān|| 52.47||
varṣam ekaṃ tato devastam uvāca tadā vibhuḥ|
kim evaṃ kliśyase vipra na tavāsti sutaḥ kvacit|| 52.48||
vyarthaste 'ayaṃ ścamastāvannāsti putrastavānagha|
sa evam ukto nirviṇṇo nirāśaḥ putrajanmani|| 52.49||
cintayāmāsa maraṇaṃ na gantuṃ svaṃ gṛhaṃ prati|
sa kāṣṭhakūṭaṃ saṃbhṛtya gṛhītvāgniṃ suduḥkhitaḥ|| 52.50||
vilapya bahuduḥkhārta ātmānaṃ dagdhum aicchata|
tasya rudrastam ālakṣya vyavasāyaṃ suduṣkaram|| 52.51||
putra putreti gambhīram adṛśya idam abravīt|
putraste bhavitā gaccha mā caivaṃ sāhasaṃ kṛthāḥ|| 52.52||
kāṣṭhakūṭeti nāmnā ca bhaviṣyati sa te sutaḥ|
atha hṛṣṭamanā vipro gatvā patnyāṃ mahātapāḥ|| 52.53||
utpādayāmāsa sutaṃ kāṣṭhakūṭaṃ mahāmunim|
saṃskṛtasya tu kālena tasya buddhirabhūt tataḥ|| 52.54||
aśakto 'ayaṃ vṛddhabhāvānmām adhyāpayituṃ pitā|
tasmādyāsyāmi cāmantrya pitaraṃ vedakāraṇāt|| 52.55||
sa gatvā mātaraṃ vipraḥ pitaraṃ ca mahāyaśāḥ|
praṇamya śirasā samyagidaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 52.56||
suto yuvābhyāṃ jāto 'ahaṃ dharmahetorna kāmataḥ|
āvāṃ tārayitā cāyaṃ tathaiva ca pitāmahān|| 52.57||
santatiścāpyavicchinnā bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|
iṣṭāṃśca lokān prāpsyāva suputreṇeti sarvathā|| 52.58||
pitR̥ṇāṃ cānṛṇau syāva ityabhīṣṭo 'asmi vāṃ sutaḥ|
so 'ahaṃ dharmeṣvakuśalaḥ śrutismṛtibahiṣkṛtaḥ|| 52.59||
kartājñānena tat karma pitaro yena duḥkhitāḥ|
bhavāṃśca niraye magnaściraṃ vatsyati duṣṭavat|| 52.60||
bhavān na dhyāpane śaktaḥ sthaviratvāddine dine|
putrasnehācca kāryācca na samyagdhārayiṣyāsi|| 52.61||
iyaṃ ca jananī nityam ekaputro 'ayam ityuta|
tvayā samyak praśāsyantaṃ naiva mām anumaṃsyate|| 52.62||
so 'aham anyaṃ tapo nityaṃ niranukrośam eva ca|
ācāryaṃ matisaṃpannaṃ saṃśrayāmīti me matiḥ|| 52.63||
na cāpi tadvyavasyāmi yuvayornāsti kaścana|
kuryādyaḥ pādayornityaṃ śuśrūṣām iti cintayan|| 52.64||
na ca nākhyayam etadvāṃ mayā cintā kṛtā śubham|
aśubhaṃ vāpi yat kiṃcidyuvāṃ mama gatiḥ parā|| 52.65||
evam uktau tu pitarau putreṇa sumahātmanā|
aśrupūrṇekṣaṇau sthitvā muhūrtam idam ūcatuḥ|
āghrāyāliṅgya saṃmṛjya snehāt priyasutau tadā|| 52.66||
bhūmanyuruvāca|
śuśrūṣā dvividhā putra pitR̥ṇāṃ dharmasaṃmitā|
yā kartavyā prayatnena sutena sumahātmanā|| 52.67||
aihikī cāṅguśuśrūṣā yā paratra ca dharmadā|
yayā taranti pitaraḥ kāmāṃścāpnuvate 'akṣayān|
tatraihikaṃ na no hīṣṭaṃ yathā hi āmuṣmikaṃ hitam|| 52.68||
tasmādāmuṣmikaṃ karma yadbhavet tat samācara|
gacchādhīṣva śrutiṃ caiva smṛtiṃ caiva sukarmaṇām|| 52.69||
suyaśovāca|
yathā te 'ayaṃ pitā putra bravīti viditātmavān|
tathā kutu yathā devo varadaste bhavedbhavaḥ|| 52.70||
udareṇa mayā duḥkhaṃ dhāritastvaṃ mahāmate|
tathā ca bahubhiḥ kleśairlabdhaḥ sarvārthasiddhaye|| 52.71||
pitrā ca tapasogreṇa prāṇāṃstyaktvātidustyajān|
mahādevādbhavā/llabdhastasya yuktaṃ samācara|| 52.72||
yathā tuṣṭau tvayā putra jīvau jīvena saṃgatau|
āvām ubhāvapi syāva tathā samyak samācara|| 52.73||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastābhyām anujñāta āghrātaścaiva mūrdhani|
pradakṣiṇam upāvṛtya jagāma sa kṛtātmavān|| 52.74||
sa jagāma tadā tābhyāṃ visṛṣṭaścyavanaṃ prati|
ṛgyajurbhyām ivotsṛṣṭā svāhutirvaruṇaṃ prati|| 52.75||
sa tam āsādya tuṣṭena tenāsau saphalaḥ kṛtaḥ|
bhāgadheyam iva prāpya devairmantraḥ purassaraḥ|| 52.76||
atha putre gate tasmin pitā diṣṭāntam īyivān|
kāṣṭhakūṭastato 'abhyetya kṛtavidyaḥ sudhārmikaḥ|| 52.77||
apaśyanmātaraṃ dīnāṃ vitoyām iva padminīm|
somahīnām iva niśām ājñāhīnām iva śriyam|
rudatīm aśrupūrṇākṣīṃ vilapantīṃ suduḥkhitām|| 52.78||
kāṣṭhakūṭastu tāṃ dṛṣṭvā duḥkhena samabhiplutām|
jayaṃta iva paulomīṃ śakre naṣṭe 'abravīdidam|| 52.79||
kāṣṭhakūṭa uvāca|
śrutaṃ mayedaṃ prāgeva kṛtaṃ caivordhvadehikam|
mā śoke mana ādhatsva eṣa dharmaḥ sanātanaḥ|| 52.80||
devānāṃ ca ṛṣīṇāṃ ca yogināṃ ca mahātmanām|
martyānāṃ kiṃ puno māto mā śucastaṃ tapodhanam|| 52.81||
ahaṃ tenātmanātmā vai sṛṣṭaḥ svenaiva tejasā|
paśya māṃ kṛtakṛtyaṃ tvaṃ gāyatrīvātmanaḥ sutam|| 52.82||
vedāḥ sarve mayādhītāḥ sāṅgopāṅgāḥ savistarāḥ|
tathopavedāḥ sarve ca adhyātmaṃ caiva kṛtsnaśaḥ|| 52.83||
yat kiṃit puruṣairjñeyaṃ tat sarvaṃ jñānam eva ca|
śrotavyaṃ ca śrutaṃ sarvam upāstāścāpi yoginaḥ|| 52.84||
anenāpi prakarṣeṇa hṛṣyamāṇā mudānvitā|
māṃ pālaya mahāsattve gāyatrīva sadā kratum|| 52.85||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śrutvā tasya vacastadvai mātā tathyaṃ mahātmanaḥ|
bhūyastareṇa duḥkhena rudatī tam uvāca ha|| 52.86||
suyaśovāca|
putra naitaddhi duḥkhaṃ me mṛtaḥ sa iti saṃmataḥ|
sarveṣāṃ prāṇinām etadvihitaṃ martyadharmiṇām|| 52.87||
sa cāpi kṛtakṛtyaśca mahātmā tapasānvitaḥ|
na tasya śocyam asmābhiriha kiṃciddhi vidyate|| 52.88||
ātmānaṃ putra śocāmi yāhaṃ tena vinā kṛtā|
tam evānu mṛtā nāsmi tavāgamanakāṃkṣiṇī|| 52.89||
nārthā na bhogasvajanā na putrā naiva bāndhavāḥ|
yoṣitāṃ tatra tiṣṭhanti patiryatrāvatiṣṭhate|| 52.90||
patiryadi tataḥ sarvaṃ nāsti kiṃcit patiṃ vinā|
sarvaṃ hi duḥkhadaṃ tāsāṃ yāsāṃ nāsti patiḥ suta|| 52.91||
idaṃ ca me puno duḥkhaṃ yat tvāṃ tena sahādya vai|
nābhinandāmi saṃhṛṣṭā sutaṃ śrīriva viṣṇunā|| 52.92||
bahuśaḥ sa hi mām āha kāṣṭhakūṭa ihaiṣyati|
kṛtavidyastatastasya varayiṣye snuṣāṃ śubhām|| 52.93||
kāśyapasyodalasyeyaṃ sutā guṇavatī bhṛśam|
tām ahaṃ varayiṣyāmi kāṣṭhakūṭasya suvratām|| 52.94||
tadā drakṣyāmi taṃ putraṃ sapatnīkaṃ dṛḍhavratam|
agnīṃścaivāhariṣyāmi patnīvantaṃ samīkṣya vai|| 52.95||
patnyāḥ kadāhaṃ putrasya pāṇigrahaṇatoṣitaḥ|
śubhāni manasā vācā vidhāsyāmi bahūnyapi|| 52.96||
evaṃ manorathavatastasya putravatastathā|
priyaputrasya naivābhūdetaddahati māṃ suta|| 52.97||
mayā tvam uktapūrvaśca gacchan vai tasya sannidhau|
jīvau yathā tvāṃ paśyāvastacca naivābhavat tathā|| 52.98||
vajrasāramayaṃ me 'adya hṛdayaṃ na hi dīryate|
yā tvāṃ paśyāmi putreha vinā tenāsatī punaḥ|| 52.99||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sā kurarī yadvadvinā patyā mahāyaśā|
vilapya bahuduḥkhārtā papāta dharaṇītale|| 52.100||
tāṃ kāṣṭhakūṭo duḥkhārtāṃ patitāṃ gatajīvitām|
visaṃjñām agninā dagdhvā vilalāpa suduḥkhitaḥ|| 52.101||
hā tāta mama durbuddheradharmajñasya caiva hi|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 52.102||
kva gato 'asi na me 'adya tvaṃ sabhāryaḥ saṃprabhāṣase|
nanu tvayāhaṃ nirdiṣṭo gacchādhīṣveti hṛṣṭavat|| 52.103||
so 'aham adyāgato 'adhītya kasmānmāṃ nābhibhāṣase|
nanu te tapasā labdhaḥ pareṇa ca samādhinā|| 52.104||
putro 'ahaṃ devadevādvai rudrāt kiṃ nābhibhāṣase|
kiṃ mayāpakṛtaṃ tāta sahabhāryasya te 'anagha|| 52.105||
yanmāṃ sahāmbayāgatya dṛḍhaṃ naivābhinandasi|
hā hato 'asmi mayaikena duṣputreṇa durātmanā|| 52.106||
arājakam idaṃ manye pitṛghnaṃ māṃ na hanti yat|
evaṃ sa vilapan vyāsa ṛṣibhirbahubhistathā|| 52.107||
saṃsthāpitaḥ samāśvaste nākarodudakakriyām|
imāṃ pratijñāṃ cakre ca ṛṣimadhye mahātapāḥ|| 52.108||
duṣkarāṃ sarvabhūtānām upaspṛśya kṛtāñjaliḥ|
adyaprabhṛti nocchvāsaṃ kariṣyāmi kathaṃcana|| 52.109||
vāyavo me śarīrasthā na cariṣyanti karhicit|
nimeṣonmeṣarahita ekapādordhvabāhumān|
kāṣṭhaloṣṭhopalībhūto bhaviṣyāmi na saṃśayaḥ|| 52.110||
rudraṃ drakṣyāmi yāvacca yāvacca pitaraṃ tathā|
sabhāryaṃ saṃprapaśyāmi tāvaccratam idaṃ mama|| 52.111||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa ṛṣibhistaistu dṛśyamāno mahātapāḥ|
maheśvaraṃ sadā dhyāyaṃstatraiva samatiṣṭhata|| 52.112||
tasya devaḥ sthitasyaivaṃ pitṛbhaktyā tathāpi ca|
tuṣṭo dine 'aṣṭame vyāsa svayam evāha śaṃkaraḥ|| 52.113||
devadeva uvāca|
kāṣṭhakūṭa prayacchāmi divyaṃ cakṣustavānagha|
paśya māṃ tvaṃ suviśrabdham adṛśyaṃ yoginām api|| 52.114||
brūhi putra varaṃ cāpi yaste hṛdi samāhitaḥ|
pradāsyāmi na sandehaḥ suniścityābhidhatsva mām|| 52.115||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa dṛṣṭvā deveśam udyantam iva bhāskaram|
papāta pādayorhṛṣṭa idaṃ covāca susvaram|| 52.116||
kāṣṭhakūṭa uvāca|
bhagavan mṛtyunā mātā pitā ca mama yojitau|
jīvetāṃ tāvubhau deva etadicchāmyahaṃ varam|| 52.117||
devadeva uvāca|
tāvubhau narakaṃ ghoraṃ prapannau mṛtyunārditau|
na tau śakyau puno jīvau kartum anyadvṛṇīṣva me|| 52.118||
kāṣṭhakūṭa uvāca|
nāham anyaṃ varaṃ deva kathaṃcidapi kāmaye|
pitrartho 'ayaṃ samārambhastadvidhatsva namastava|| 52.119||
devadeva uvāca|
śarīraṃ cenmṛtasyāsti tacchakyaṃ jīvitena hi|
saṃyojayitum adyaiva dagdhasyaitanna vidyate|| 52.120||
tayorna cāsti vai deho na cānyat karaṇaṃ tathā|
yādṛk ca sa pitā tubhyaṃ bhavāṃstādṛk śarīrataḥ|
śarīram etat tvaṃ yaccha tato jīvau bhaviṣyatas|| 52.121||
kāṣṭhakūṭa uvāca|
tābhyāṃ vai nāsti kartavyaṃ kartavyaṃ cenmataṃ bhavet (?)|
śarīraṃ ca vinā dṛṣṭam utthānaṃ vai dhruvasya tu (?)|| 52.122||
na cāpi me śarīreṇa vinā tābhyāṃ ratiḥ prabho|
tasmādgṛhāṇa deveśa śarīraṃ yadi manyase|| 52.123||
tasyaivedaṃ tahādeva aṅgādaṅgaṃ samutthitam|
tasmādyacchasva deveśa na me kāryam anena hi|| 52.124||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaḥ prahasya ṛṣisattama|
prītātmā pratyuvācedaṃ yuyukṣustaṃ śubhena hi|| 52.125||
devadeva uvāca|
parīkṣeyaṃ kṛtā putra tava dharmavṛtāṃ vara|
pitṛbhaktyānayā samyak tuṣṭo 'asmi śṛṇu me vacaḥ|| 52.126||
akṣayaścāvyayaścāpi jarāmṛtyuvivarjitaḥ|
aiśvaryeṇa ca saṃyuktaḥ priyo me gaṇapo bhavān|| 52.127||
kāṣṭhakūṭa iti khyātaḥ sarvayogabalānvitaḥ|
kāmagena vimānena matkṛtena cariṣyasi|| 52.128||
ime ca ṛṣayaḥ sarva āśrame 'asmiṃstapasvinaḥ|
tavaivānucarā bhūtvā bhaviṣyanti gaṇeśvarāḥ|| 52.129||
akṣayāścāvyayāścaiva mahāyogabalānvitāḥ|
aiśvaryeṇa ca tulyāste bhaviṣyanti na saṃśayaḥ|| 52.130||
ayaṃ ca te pitā putra bhūmanyuḥ saha bhāryayā|
tavaivānucaro bhūtvā tvatsamaḥ samupasthitaḥ|| 52.131||
śvetaṃ ca parvataṃ divyaṃ vimānairupaśobhitam|
kāmagaṃ saṃprayacchāmi nivāsaṃ svargasannibham|| 52.132||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devo 'anugṛhya tam ūrjitam|
jagāma mandaraṃ bhūyaḥ so 'apīṣṭaṃ deśam āvrajat|| 52.133||
yavaddevī tapoyuktā pituḥ śikharam āsthitā|
tāvaddeva idaṃ sarvaṃ cakāra kathitaṃ hi yat|| 52.134||
ya idaṃ devadevasya ceṣṭitaṃ śṛṇuyānnaraḥ|
śrāvayīta dvijān vāpi na sa durgatim āpnuyāt|| 52.135||
nityam etadadhīyānaḥ śuciḥ prayatamānasaḥ|
dehabhedaṃ samāsādya rudralokaṃ sa gacchati|| 52.136||
ya imaṃ bahupāpanāśanaṃ paramaṃ rudrasamīpayojanam|
paṭhate ca gaṇaprasādhanaṃ sa mṛto yāti na dīnasaṃbhavam|| 52.137||
iti skandapurāṇe kāṣṭhakūṭamahābhāgyaṃ nāma
dvipañcāśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 52.52||

tripañcāśattamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
devī bhagavatī sā hi himavattanayāvyayā|
kiyantaṃ kālam acarat tapaḥ paramaduścaram|| 53.1||
kathaṃ labdhavatī cāpi varaṃ varaśatāraṇiḥ|
etadicchāmi kathitaṃ sarvaṃ vai dvijasattama|| 53.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu kāle vyatīte hi tapo devyāḥ suduścaram|
prayatā prāñjalirbhūtvā samādhāya manastathā|| 53.3||
divākare 'abhisandhāya cakṣuṣī mana eva ca|
tasthau vṛkṣāvabaddheva dārvarcānimiṣekṣaṇā|| 53.4||
suvarcalena sādityam īkṣatī paryavartata|
ekapādordhvabāhuśca nirucchvāsā babhūva ha|| 53.5||
divyaṃ varṣasahasraṃ sā niścalopalavat sthitā|
vyāghradvitīyā rudrāṇī tapoyuktā śubhavratā|| 53.6||
na cāsyā glānirabhavanna balakṣaya eva vā|
pūrvavacca hi sā devī tapaso vāvatiṣṭatha|| 53.7||
tasyāstapaḥprabhāveṇa sarvaṃ sasthāṇujaṅgamam|
abhāvopahataṃ yadvajjagadārtam atiṣṭhata|| 53.8||
nātidīpto 'abhavat sūryasścandramā na prakāśate|
jyotīṃṣi timirāṇi āsan vyomni siddhā na yānti ca|| 53.9||
mamluśca devamālyāni vimānāni ca petire|
svarge 'api na sukhaṃ teṣām autsukyaṃ cāpi jāyate|| 53.10||
dhūmāyanti diśaḥ sarvāstrailkoyaṃ caiva kṛtsnaśaḥ|
vidyādhṛtāṃ gatirbhagnā prajvalanti āyudhāni ca|| 53.11||
mṛgā vyāghrāśca siṃhāśca viḍālolūkamūṣikāḥ|
pannagā nakulāścaiva ekasthāḥ saṃcarantyuta|| 53.12||
tato devāḥ samāgatya ūcuḥ sarve parasparam|
viparyayo 'ayaṃ nākasmāt trailokyasyāsya dṛśyate|| 53.13||
kāraṇaṃ mahadatrāsti nedaṃ niṣkāraṇaṃ bhavet|
tasmādvayam ajānanta etaṃ sarvaviparyayam|| 53.14||
kiṃ tiṣṭhāmaḥ samudvignā gacchāma brahmaṇo 'antikam|
ityuktvā te surāḥ sarve bṛhaspatipurogamāḥ|| 53.15||
vairājabhavanaṃ gatvā brahmāṇaṃ saṃpraṇemire|
pūjitā brahmaṇā samyagupaviṣṭā yathārhataḥ|| 53.16||
pṛṣṭāstenāgame hetum ūcurhṛcchokapīḍitāḥ|
bhagava/llokatattvaṃ ca sarvaṃ pratyakṣavadvibhoḥ|| 53.17||
loko 'ayaṃ viparīto 'adya kimarthaṃ śaṃsa naḥ prabho|
teṣāṃ tad vacanaṃ śrutvā bhītānāṃ sarvayogavit|| 53.18||
uvāca madhuraṃ ślakṣṇam idaṃ gambhīravadvacaḥ|
eṣā haimavatī devī rudrāṇī lokadhāriṇī|
tapaścarati yuktātmā yogam āsthāya niścalam|| 53.19||
adya varṣasahasraṃ hi divyaṃ tasyāḥ samādhinā|
varṣāṇāṃ dve śate caiva tathānyaccharadāṃ śatam|| 53.20||
tapaścarantyā yogena tasyaiṣa tapasaḥ surāḥ|
prabhāvo yena lokānāṃ viparītatvam āgatam|| 53.21||
devā ūcus|
yadi tasyāḥ prabhāveṇa mahotpātabhayaṃ tvidam|
ato bhūyo dahellokāṃstasmāt tāṃ sannivāraya|| 53.22||
sā hi devī tapoyuktā ato bhūyo vibhāvarī|
lokānimān sahāsmābhirdahedapi na saṃśayaḥ|| 53.23||
tasmāllokahitārthāya asmākaṃ vacanādapi|
tathā kuru yathā sādhvī vinivarteta śobhanā|| 53.24||
pitāmaha uvāca|
evaṃ bhavatu gacchadhvaṃ nirvṛtā bhavatānaghāḥ|
varapradāneneṣṭena rudrāṇīṃ sthāpayāmyaham|| 53.25||
gateṣvatha tu deveṣu brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
vimānaṃ kāñcanaṃ śubhraṃ vedikāśatasaṃkulam|| 53.26||
kiṅkiṇījālasannaddhaṃ muktādāmāvabhāsitam|
indranīlamayaiḥ stambhairjālairjāmbūnadaistathā|| 53.27||
ghaṃṭābhirviśvarūpābhiḥ samantāt parivāritam|
vajrendranīlavaidūryamahānīlādibhāsitam|| 53.28||
stūpikābhiśca yogyābhiḥ sphāṭikāṅkābhirāvṛtam|
sarvalohamayaṃ tadvai svayaṃ devena nirmitam|| 53.29||
pañca bhūtamayaṃ taddhi prakṛtistham athāpi ca|
śabdābhijālasambaddhaṃ ghaṇṭhendriyasuśabdavat|| 53.30||
muktādāmāṣṭakairyuktaṃ kiṅkiṇīṣoḍaśāvṛtam|
viṃśatirvedikāścātra vimānaṃ tanmahāprabham|| 53.31||
śatārddhalakṣaṇairdivyairmaṇibhūmistathācitam|
āsanairbahubhiryuktaṃ lokasthānaiḥ samantataḥ|| 53.32||
āruroha vimānaṃ tadbrahmā svamunibhiḥ saha|
vedaiḥ saha tathā mantraiḥ śāstraiḥ sarvaistathaiva ca|| 53.33||
madhye tasyāsanaṃ divyaṃ svarṇapadmopagaṃ dṛḍham|
sukhopaviṣṭastatrāsau brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|| 53.34||
tasya pārśve tu sāvitrī gāyatrī caiva suprabhā|
ṛgvedo dakṣiṇenāsya yajurvedaśca paścime|| 53.35||
uttare sāmavedastu agrato 'artharvaṇastathā|
prāyaścittāni dharmāśca niyamāśca tapāṃsi ca|| 53.36||
dānāni ca vicitrāṇi kratavaḥ seṣṭayastathā|
saptavyāhṛtayaḥ puṇyāstathā lokāśca sarvaśaḥ|| 53.37||
parvatāścaiva nadyaśca tathā lokasya mātaraḥ|
lokapālāḥ prajādhyakṣā dakṣo dharmastathaiva ca|| 53.38||
bhṛguratrirvasiṣṭhaśca pulastyaḥ pulahaḥ kratuḥ|
marīciraṅgirāścaiva ruciścaiva mahāyaśās|| 53.39||
ṛbhuḥ sanātanaścaiva virājaśca mahātapāḥ|
pitaraścaiva devāśca brahmaṇo yāḥ prasūtayaḥ|| 53.40||
pṛthivī vāyurākāśam āpo jyotistathaiva ca|
ete caiva yathoddiṣṭāḥ sāgarā diśa eva ca|| 53.41||
vidyāśca dharmakārāśca agrataste 'avatasthire|
brahmadaṇḍaśca daṇḍaśca kalaśaḥ kāñcanastathā|| 53.42||
kamaṇḍaluśca tasyāsīt pārśvayorubhayorapi|
yajñopavītaṃ śrīmacca .oṃkāraśca tathāgrataḥ|| 53.43||
akṣasūtraṃ ca yogaśca japyaṃ caivāgrataḥ sthitāḥ|
svāhā svadhā vaṣaṭ vauṣadagniścaitāni pārśvataḥ|| 53.44||
yamāśca niyamāścaiva sādhanāni bahūni ca|
dharmasyaitāni sarvāṇi pārśvasthānyabhavaṃstataḥ|| 53.45||
dayā kṛpātha dānaṃ ca śraddhā caiva hriyā saha|
ṛṣīṇāṃ pārśvagāḥ sarvā dakṣiṇā yajñapārśvagā|| 53.46||
tato devāśca ye kecidbrahmalokanivāsinaḥ|
sarve samadhiruhyāśu samantādavatasthire|| 53.47||
evaṃ teṣu vimānaṃ tat samārūḍheṣu sarvaśaḥ|
sukhāsīneṣu sarveṣu brahmā samanucodayat|| 53.48||
taccoditaṃ yogavidagragāminā mahāvimānottamasarvagāminā|
yayau prabhāveṇa manonugāminā yathā manaḥ sarvasṛjeva hetunā|| 53.49||
iti skandapurāṇe devīvarapradāne brahmaṇaḥ prayāṇaṃ nāma
tripañcāśattamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 53.52||

catuṣpañcāśattamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastena vimānena sarvasṛk caturānanaḥ|
jagāma mandaraṃ dhīmān vicitropalakandaram|| 54.1||
sa tam āsādya vistīrṇam anaupamyam atiprabham|
dūrāddṛṣṭisukhaṃ dṛṣṭvā sabhāsthānidam abravīt|| 54.2||
idaṃ rudragṛhaṃ śubhram adṛśyaṃ sukṛtām api|
devānām api paśyadhvaṃ bhāskarākāravarcasam|| 54.3||
idaṃ praviśya devānāṃ yajñaśrīrnāpasarpati|
jayaśca nityaṃ yuddheṣu dharmaśca sumahānapi|| 54.4||
etat sṛṣṭaṃ svayaṃ tena manasānupamadyuti|
na hyasya sadṛśaṃ kiṃcidaṇḍe 'asmin vidyate gṛham|| 54.5||
idaṃ praviśya dharmātmā bhūyo duḥkhaṃ na vindati|
na cāpi janma prāpnoti nityam aiśvaryago hi saḥ|| 54.6||
anirdeśyam idaṃ yogādyoginām api nityaśaḥ
anyastu kuta evedaṃ varṇayīta mahānapi|| 54.7||
etadasmadvimānasya vāyunābhyāhataṃ ruṣā|
vardhate giriṇā sārdhaṃ vindhyasya śikharaṃ yathā|| 54.8||
etadasmadvimānasya mārgam āvṛtyadhiṣṭhitam|
ūrdhvaṃ tiryagadhastācca devadevasya tejasā|| 54.9||
etadandhaṃ tamaḥ kṛtvā megho 'asau jīvanaḥ svayam (?)|
vajrodyatakaraḥ sragvī pratyudyātyabhinādayan|| 54.10||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devo brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
viṣṭabhya tadvimānāgryam avatasthe kṛtāñjaliḥ|| 54.11||
tuṣṭāva ca tadā devaṃ śarvam ugraṃ kapardinam|
te caiva ṛṣayaḥ sarve vimānasthāḥ susaṃyatāḥ|| 54.12||
prakāśaṃ cakrire sarvaṃ jagat sthāvarajaṃgamam|
tataḥ sa meghaḥ svaṃ sthānam agamadvṛṣṭisarjanaḥ|| 54.13||
diśaśca vimalāḥ sarvāḥ prakāśaścābhavadbhṛśam|
taṃ japantaṃ viditvā ca bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|| 54.14||
nandinaṃ dvāradeśastham idam āha sureśvaraḥ|
eṣa brahmā vimānena mām iha draṣṭum āgataḥ|| 54.15||
brūhi yenāgato 'asīha kāryeṇa vidito 'asi me|
kuru tadgaccha śīghraṃ tu kālastasyāyam āgatas|| 54.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto rudreṇa nandī pramathanāyakaḥ
dvāḥstha eva vimānasthaṃ brahmāṇam idam abravīt|| 54.17||
nandyuvāca|
yūyaṃ jñātā bhagavatā yena kāryeṇa cāgatāḥ|
kurudhvaṃ kila tacchīghraṃ kālo 'ayaṃ tasya vartate|| 54.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa kṛtvā manasā namaskāraṃ hi śambhave|
pradakṣiṇam upāvṛtya mandaraṃ prajagāma ha|| 54.19||
sa mandaragiriṃ sarvaṃ parihṛtya mahāmanāḥ
śākadvīpasya madhyena jambūdvīpam upāgamat|| 54.20||
sa dṛśyamāno devaiśca munibhiśca yatavrataiḥ|
himavantaṃ giriśreṣṭham upāgamyedam abravīt|| 54.21||
etaddhimavataḥ śṛṅgam ucchritaṃ kāntimat sthitam|
yugāntādityasaṃkāśaṃ dūrāt samabhilakṣyate|| 54.22||
atra sā jagato dhātrī dhātrī putram ivaurasam|
pālayantī jagat sarvaṃ tapastapyati śailajā|| 54.23||
aho nu śikharaṃ puṇyaṃ bhāgyavaccāpi sarvathā|
yadenaṃ giriputryarthe varairyokṣyati kāmahā|| 54.24||
paśyadhvaṃ tapaso vīryaṃ devyāḥ sucaritasya vai|
yadetacchikharaṃ dṛṣṭvā na paśyāma puno bhavam|| 54.25||
sa evaṃ kathayanneva vimānena caturmukhaḥ|
ṛṣibhiḥ sahitaḥ sarvaiḥ śikharadvāram āgataḥ|| 54.26||
tatrainaṃ rudrasacivā udyatāyudhapāṇayaḥ|
bhartsayanto 'abhyavartanta tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti vādinaḥ|| 54.27||
tān brahmā ślakṣṇayā vācā sāntvapūrvam uvāca ha|
praśaṃsamānastān sarvān prāñjaliryuktamānasaḥ|| 54.28||
brahmovāca|
yūyaṃ sarve mahātmāna aiśvaryeṇa samanvitāḥ|
akṣayā hyanarāścaiva tathāpratihatāśca ha|| 54.29||
mahāyogabalopetā ajayyā yudhi kenacit|
ko yuṣmānativarteta śakro 'api pravareśvarāḥ|| 54.30||
devadevājñayā yo 'aham āgato mandarādiha|
devyā varapradānārtham anujñā kriyatāṃ mama|| 54.31||
gaṇeśvarā ūcuḥ|
devyās dātā svayaṃ devo varāniṣṭān mahāmanāḥ|
varaṃ hi devī tvanyasmānmanasāpi na cintayet|| 54.32||
śakto devo 'anugrahītuṃ jagat sarvaṃ maheśvaraḥ|
tvām apyeṣo 'anugṛhṇāti kim u devīṃ jagatpatiḥ|| 54.33||
pitāmaha uvāca|
aśakto na mahādevo varaṃ dātuṃ mahāmanāḥ|
ya evaṃ cintayeddevaṃ na bhavet sa kathaṃcana|| 54.34||
na devī bhagavatpārśvādicchate kila pārvatī|
varāniṣṭāṃstato devo mām iha praiṣayacchivaḥ|| 54.35||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha te yuktamanaso yuktaṃ pratyakṣam īśvarāḥ|
maheśvaram apaśyanta kṛtānujñaṃ ca lokapam|| 54.36||
niyuktāśca punaḥ sarve brahmāṇaṃ lokakāraṇam|
ūcurgaṇeśvarāṃstatra viditārthā mahāmune|| 54.37||
preṣito devadevena jñāto 'asmābhiḥ pitāmaha|
tvaṃ viśasvādhunā deva pārvatyā varaditsayā|| 54.38||
avatīrya vimānāt tu tataḥ śīghraṃ pitāmahaḥ|
nililye śikhare tasmin nānādhāruvicitrite|| 54.39||
atha sopaladhātunirjharo girirājo 'atimahāśiloccayaḥ|
vinisṛṣṭadivākarāmalo didive divya ivodayācalaḥ|| 54.40||
iti skandapurāṇe devyā varapradāne brahmāgamanaṃ nāma
catuṣpañcāśattamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 54.54||

pañcapañcāśattamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha taṃ sahasāyātam apaśyat sācalātmajā|
ṛṣibhistairmahābhāgaiḥ samantāt parivāritam|| 55.1||
raśmibhistejasāṃ yoniṃ madhyāhna iva bhāskaram|
sā tam argheṇa pādyena madhuparkeṇa caiva hi|
pūjayāmāsa rudrāṇī caturvaktram upāgatam|| 55.2||
brahmovāca|
lokasya jananī bhūtvā dhārayitvā jagat tathā|
kim idaṃ tapasā bhūyo lokaṃ dagdhum ihecchasi|| 55.3||
mā sṛṣṭvā jagadetat tvaṃ tapasyantī vināśaya|
buddhvaivaṃ dhārayasvemaṃ lokaṃ devi namastava|| 55.4||
tvatto rudreṇa loko 'ayam ahaṃ caiva purānaghe|
sṛṣṭāḥ smo varade devi mā naḥ kṛtvā vināśaya|| 55.5||
tapasā tava rudrāṇi jagat sthāvarajaṅgamam|
tapyate grīṣmamadhyāhne jalāt padmam ivoddhṛtam|| 55.6||
kiṃ vā te hṛdaye devi yadyapi syāt suduṣkaram|
varaṃ vṛṇīhi sarvāṇi dātāsmi himavatsute|| 55.7||
devyuvāca|
varado 'asi yadīśāna mama deva caturmukha|
ayaṃ bhakto 'anuraktaśca mama nityaṃ priyaḥ prabho|| 55.8||
vyāghro 'asya tāvadyacchasva tato dāsyasi me varam|
adya varṣasahasraṃ vai sthitasyāsya mamāgrataḥ|| 55.9||
dhyāyato nimiṣasyaiva stabdhakarṇasya lokapa|
asmai dhatsva varaṃ deva nāsmi tāvadvarārthinī|| 55.10||
pitāmaha uvāca|
eṣa tiryagdurātmā ca tvāṃ bhakṣayitum āgataḥ|
nāsya śuddhaṃ mano devi krūro 'ayaṃ pāpacetanaḥ|
paśyainaṃ duṣṭamanasaṃ nāsya śreyo manastvayi|| 55.11||
sanatkumāras_uvāca|
atha sā tadvacaḥ śrutvā rudrāṇī lokabhāvanī|
divyena cakṣuṣāpaśyadajñānāt kṛtasāhasam|| 55.12||
ananyabhaktaḥ pūrvaṃ ca jātidoṣeṇa dūṣitaḥ|
viditārthā tato bhūtvā uvāca himatsutā|| 55.13||
bhagavan ko hi lokeṣu tiryaktve sati niścalaḥ|
stabdhakarṇekṣaṇo divyam aho 'apyekam abhojanaḥ|| 55.14||
avatiṣṭheta kiṃ yo yaṃ sahasrmāvatiṣṭhata|
varṣāṇāṃ sumahātejā nāyaṃ tiryakṣu saṃskṛtaḥ|| 55.15||
bhavatvayaṃ duṣṭacetāstvaduṣṭo vā mahābalaḥ|
mamānugrāhya ityeva varo hyasya pradīyatām|| 55.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaścaturvaktraḥ pitāmahaḥ|
uvāca vacanaṃ devīm ṛṣīṇāṃ śṛṇvatāṃ tadā|| 55.17||
āryāṇāṃ dasyavo 'apīha saṃsargāt siddhim āpnuyuḥ|
yathāyaṃ krūrakarmāpi siddhiṃ prāpsyatyanuttamām|| 55.18||
tasmādāryāḥ sadā sevyā nityaṃ pāpakṛtāpi hi|
siddhim eti naraḥ kṣipram apāpānāṃ samīpagaḥ|| 55.19||
anugrāhyastavānindye pāpo 'ayaṃ duṣṭacetanaḥ|
ato 'asmai brūhi deveśe varo yastava rocate|| 55.20||
devyuvāca|
amaro jarayā tyakto 'akṣayaścāvyayastathā|
mahāyogabalopeto mahadaiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|
gaṇeśvaro mameṣṭaśca bhavatveṣa yadīcchasi|| 55.21||
pitāmaha uvāca|
evaṃ bhavatu bhadraṃ te sarvam etadbhaviṣyati|
jānāsi brahmabandhūnāṃ brahmadattasya mantriṇam|| 55.22||
tvayi bhaktiḥ purāpyasya śāpādvyāghragatiṃ gataḥ|
pañcālasya ca yakṣo 'ayaṃ pratīharo 'abhavat purā|| 55.23||
tvayā mayā yadasyāsya kṛteyaṃ nandirīdṛśī|
tasmādgamiṣyati khyātiṃ somanandīti nāmataḥ|| 55.24||
yaścainaṃ kīrtayeddurge kāntāreṣu bhayeṣu ca|
śārdūlasiṃhadvīpibhyo na bhayaṃ tasya jāyate|| 55.25||
vada tvam api ceśāni yaste priyamanorathaḥ|
yāvaddadāmi sarvaṃ te niyogāt pārameśvarāt|| 55.26||
devyuvāca|
icchāmi bhagavan divyaṃ varṇaṃ kanakasaprabham|
gaurīti loke khyātā ca bhaveyaṃ kamalodbhava|| 55.27||
pitāmaha uvāca|
evam astu jaganmātaryadicchasi tapodhane|
anyaṃ varaya bhadraṃ te varaṃ devi dadāmi te|| 55.28||
mahaddhīdaṃ tapastaptaṃ bhavatyā lokabhāvanam|
nānurūpo varastasya tasmādanyo 'api mṛgyatām|| 55.29||
devyuvāca|
icchāmi bhagavan putraṃ sarvadharmabhṛtāṃ varam|
mahābalaṃ mahotsāhaṃ sarvalokanamaskṛtam|| 55.30||
pitāmaha uvāca|
putraste bhavitā devi mahāyogabalānvitaḥ|
ajeyaḥ sarvabhūtānām aṣṭaiśvaryaguṇānvitaḥ|| 55.31||
jeyā hantā tathā deṣṭā ajaro 'abadhya eva ca|
anādeyaśca satataṃ sarveṣāṃ prāṇināṃ varaḥ|| 55.32||
sadā balo 'atha subhago dharmajño dharmavatsalaḥ|
devabrāhmaṇagoptā ca vidvān sarvajña eva ca|| 55.33||
ṣaṇmukho dvādaśabhujaḥ śaktipāṇistathaiva ca|
brahmaṇyaśca śāraṇyaśca devadviṭsaṃghahā tathā|| 55.34||
ayonijo mahātejā lokānāṃ sukhakṛcca hi|
śanairetaduvācāsau tataśca virarāma ha|| 55.35||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
varān sa dattvā deveśaḥ kṛtvā cāpi pradakṣiṇām|
vimānaṃ taṃ samāruhya svaṃ lokam agamat tadā|| 55.36||
rudrāṇyapi gate tasmin somanandipuraḥsaraḥ|
sthitākāśaṃ samāsthāya jayantena śacī yathā|
tathā sā bhāti rudrāṇī somanandipuraḥsarā|| 55.38||
ya imaṃ paṭhate sadā vipaścit puruṣaḥ prātaratandrito hi kaścit|
kurute na bhayaṃ hi somanandirvaradastasya haraśca somanandī|| 55.39||
iti skandapurāṇe somanandidevyorvarapradānaṃ nāma
pañcapañcāśattamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 55.55||

ṣaṭpañcāśattamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsovāca|
bhagavan yat tvayākhyātaṃ pūrvaṃ narakavarṇane|
duṣkṛtaṃ karma kṛtvā tu narā narakagāminaḥ|| 56.1||
bhavanti sukṛtāḥ sarve svargasaukhyasamāyutāḥ|
brāhmaṇā duṣkṛtaṃ kṛtvā gatvā durgatim āpadam|| 56.2||
kathaṃ bhūyaḥ samāyānti svargasaukhyaphalaṃ mahat|
yonīrvā katham āgamya bahvīḥ saṃkarajātiṣu|
bhūyaḥ sukṛtino bhūtvā prāpnuvanti śubhāṃ gatim|| 56.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vyāsa purāvṛttaṃ daśārṇeṣu tu yacchrutam|
saptānāṃ dvijaśiṣyāṇām aśubhaṃ śubham eva ca|| 56.4||
āsīt suparvā vikhyātaḥ kauśiko brāhmaṇaḥ śuciḥ|
dhārmikaśca vadānyaśca nidvān vipraiḥ sapūjitaḥ|| 56.5||
tasya śiṣyā babhūvurhi sapta durmedhasaśca te|
guruśuśrūṣaṇe saktā nāmatastān nibodha me|| 56.6||
ātreyaḥ kaṇḍaro nāma upamanyuśca dāmanaḥ|
śāṇḍilyaścaiva hālo 'abhūdgārgyaśca vidalastathā|| 56.7||
śauśiro gautamaścaiva daṇḍakīlaśca kāśyapaḥ|
vidarbhaścaiva hārīta itīme sapta viśrutāḥ|| 56.8||
upādhyāyo 'atha tān viprān provācedaṃ mahātapāḥ|
acirādgāmito gatvā yājyadattāṃ surūpiṇīm|| 56.9||
gatvānayata homārthe śīghraṃ māhiṣmatīṃ purīm|
ta evam uktāstenaiva māhiṣmatyāstvatandritāḥ|| 56.10||
gām ādāya nivartanto mṛttikāvatim antaśaḥ|
anāvṛṣṭyā tataste tu durbhikṣe parivartati|| 56.11||
kṣudhāparigatāḥ sarva kiṃbhakṣāḥ sambabhūvire|
saptame 'ahani saṃjāte nirāhārāḥ suduḥkhitāḥ|| 56.12||
amantrayanta gām etāṃ bhakṣayāma kim āsyate|
teṣāṃ yaḥ kaṇḍharo nāma ātreyakulasambhavaḥ|| 56.13||
sa tānuvāca mā dhenuṃ bhakṣayāma gurorimām|
gurorarthe hi naḥ ślāghyā mṛtyurapyavicakṣaṇāḥ|| 56.14||
mā guroḥ krodhanirdagdhā yāsyāma nidhanaṃ vayam|
te yadā tadvaco naiva jagṛhuḥ kṣutprapīḍitāḥ|| 56.15||
sa tadovāca bhūyastānidaṃ vacanam arthavat|
yadi vo 'avadhṛtaṃ viprā bhakṣaṇe 'asyāstapodhanāḥ|| 16
mā vṛthā bhakṣayāmaināṃ pitrarthe prokṣayāmahe|
mā no doṣadvayeneha lopo bhavatu śobhanāḥ|| 56.17||
evaṃ hyalpena doṣeṇa vayaṃ yokṣyema sarvathā|
ta evam uktāḥ samyak tu vacastasyāvadhārya ca|| 56.18||
prokṣayāmāsuravyagrā pitrarthe tāṃ pasyasvinīm|
tataḥ saṃskṛtya vidhivannivedya ca mahāmune|| 56.19||
hutāgnayastato bhūtvā pratyekam upabhujya ca|
vatsam ekaṃ gale baddhvā āninyurgurave tadā|| 56.20||
atha dṛṣṭvā sa taṃ vatsaṃ dhenuṃ papraccha tān dvijaḥ|
ta ūcuḥ pathi śārdūlo 'avadhīt tām iti nirghṛṇāḥ|| 56.21||
atha teṣāṃ vacaḥ śrutvā śaṅkayā ca durātmanām|
divyena cakṣuṣāpaśyadbhakṣitāṃ tairmahātapāḥ|| 56.22||
sataḥ sa roṣādraktāśo nirdahanniva tāṃstadā|
uvāca vatsaṃ dṛṣṭvā ca kṛpayā bhṛśaduḥkhitaḥ|| 56.23||
yuṣmābhirbhakṣitā sā hi tathyaṃ na kathitaṃ ca me|
karmaṇā tena tasmādvo gatiḥ kaṣṭā bhaviṣyati|| 56.24||
prasāditaḥ sa taiḥ śiṣyairbrāhmaṇaḥ sumahādyutiḥ|
kṛpayā sa ca tān āha bhūyaḥ sarvānidaṃ vacaḥ|| 56.25||
yaduktaṃ tanmayā tathyaṃ na tanmithyā bhaviṣyati|
yeṣāṃ tu kṛtavantaḥ sthaste 'adhyavasyanti yacchubham|| 56.26||
matsamīpe ca na stheyam idānīṃ vaḥ kathaṃcana|
dṛṣṭvā vatsam imaṃ bālaṃ mā vo dhakṣyāmi gacchata|| 56.27||
atha te sahitāḥ sarve naṣṭasaṃjñā vicetasaḥ|
kālena samayujyanta cintayanto gurorvacaḥ|| 56.28||
daśārṇā nāma sā vyāsa sarit puṇyajalā śubhā|
tasyāstīre vanaṃ divyaṃ viśrutaṃ tat subhāsvaram|| 56.29||
tatra vyādho 'abhavacchūraḥ kṣupako nāma vīryavān|
tasya putrābhavaṃste vai citakāyāṃ mahābalāḥ|| 56.30||
citakā saṃprasūtā tu putrāṃstān sapta saṃmatān|
vyādhāḥ sarve 'abhavaṃste vai caitakā iti viśrutāḥ|| 56.31||
caranti sadhanuṣkāste nighnanto mṛgapakṣiṇaḥ|
siṃhān vyāghrān gajāṃścaiva varāhādīṃśca sarvaśaḥ|| 56.32||
teṣāṃ nāmāni yāni sma vyādhatve tāni me śṛṇu|
kāṇḍāro 'arjunako nāma damanaḥ siṃhako 'abhavat|| 56.33||
hālo 'abhūdvyāghrakaścaiva vidalaḥ śarabhastathā|
śaiśiro himavāṃścaiva hastiko daṇḍakīlakaḥ|| 56.34||
vidarbho vajrakaścaiva nāmānyetāni teṣu hi|
ekaśaste 'aṭavīṃ ghorāṃ caranti piśitāśanāḥ|| 56.35||
hiṃsrāḥ sattvāntakāḥ sarve yoniṃ duṣṭām upāgatāḥ|
kadācidvicarantaste mṛgān ghnantastathaiva ca|| 56.36||
upādhyāyāśramaṃ prāptāḥ karmaṇā sukṛtena ha|
tatra teṣāṃ bhayodvignāḥ sarva evābhavan mṛgāḥ|| 56.37||
mṛgān bhītān samālakṣya sa vipraḥ sumahātapāḥ|
nyavaikṣata diśaḥ sarvā vyādhāṃścāpaśyadāgatān|| 56.38||
svaśiṣyāṃstān parijñāya dhyānādvyādhatvam āgatān|
provāca karuṇāviṣṭasteṣām eva śubhepsayā|| 56.39||
śuśrūṣitaḥ purā viprairyuṣmābhiraham ādarāt|
karmaṇā tena cedānīṃ govadhyākṛtaśāpataḥ|| 56.40||
vyādhatvam iha samprāptāḥ kutsitaṃ hiṃsravṛtti yat|
sā ca gauḥ pitṛkāryeṇa bhakṣitā vo na hiṃsayā|| 56.41||
tasmādyūyam ito bhraṣṭā jātismaraṇasaṃyutāḥ|
mṛgāḥ kālañjare bhūtvā cakravākāḥ punaḥ sare|| 56.42||
dvīpe tataḥ puno haṃsā bhūtvā vai mānase hrade|
bhūyaśca mānuṣā bhūtvā jātau jātau sacetanāḥ|| 56.43||
yogayuktā mahātmāno matprasādādatandritāḥ|
sarvakilbiṣanirmuktā brahmalokam avāpsyatha|| 56.44||
etacchrutvā tatasteṣāṃ pūrvā smṛtirajāyata|
upādhyāyo 'ayam asmākam iti buddhau tadābhavat|| 56.45||
tataḥ karma jugupsantaḥ pūrvajātikṛtaṃ ca yat|
pradakṣiṇam upāvṛtya daśārṇām abhito yayuḥ|| 56.46||
daśārṇātīram āsādya saṃmantrya ca parasparam|
jātiṃ pūrvāṃ smarantaste mṛtyum eva pravavrire|| 56.47||
niścitānāṃ tatasteṣāṃ kāṇḍaro yo 'abhavaddvijaḥ|
vyādho 'arjunakanāmā sa idaṃ vacanam abravīt || 56.48||
bhavanto yanmayā pūrvam uktāstanna kṛtaṃ hi vaḥ|
idānīṃ samanuprāptaṃ māvamanyata me vacaḥ|| 56.49||
śreyo vo 'ahaṃ pravakṣyāmi śṛṇudhvaṃ kurutaiva ca|
jātim etāṃ vimokṣyāma yena hāsyāma na smṛtim|| 56.50||
putrānicchanti pitaraḥ puṣṭyarthaṃ tāraṇāya ca|
vayaṃ ca janitāstena vyādhena sumahātmanā|| 56.51||
saṃvarddhitāśca kleśena mātrā pitrā tathaiva ca|
anāpṛcchya kathaṃ tau tu mṛtyum icchāmahe vayam|| 56.52||
te yūyaṃ yadi manyadhvaṃ tau āpṛcchya visarjitāḥ|
yokṣyāma śreyasātmānam etadvo hitam uttamam|| 56.53||
na cedvisarjayetāṃ tau tayoḥ śuśrūṣaṇe ratāḥ|
tatastāvaddhi tisṭhāmo yāvat kālena tau mṛtau|| 56.54||
tato vayaṃ kṛtātmāno hyanṛṇāḥ sarvathāpi ca|
gamiṣyāmo gatiṃ puṇyām etannaḥ śreya uttamam|| 56.55||
evam astviti te sarve gṛhītvā tasya tadvacaḥ|
cintayantaḥ puro janma gṛhānevābhijagmire|| 56.56||
tān āgatān pitā dṛṣṭvā mātā ca citakā tadā|
tuṣṭyā paramayā yuktā idaṃ tān ūcaturvacaḥ|| 56.57||
putrakāḥ sucirādadya yūyam abhyāgatā gṛham|
adyāvāṃ sudṛḍhaṃ mūḍhau kiṃ ciraṃ kṛtam ityuta|| 56.58||
citakovāca|
kṣudhāviṣṭaḥ pitā vo 'adya putrasnehena putrakāḥ|
nātti māṃsam idaṃ pakvaṃ surāṃ ca na pibatyayam|| 56.59||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te 'api jātiṃ jugupsantaḥ sarve vai pāpayonayaḥ|
idam ūcuḥ kṣupaṃ caiva citakāṃ ca śubhaṃ vacaḥ|| 56.60||
bhavanto 'aśnantvavighnena puṣṭaye śāntaye 'api ca|
nāśnīmo vayam adyeha śvo bhokṣyāmo na saṃśayaḥ|| 56.61||
tatastau vṛddhabhāvena na bubhukṣāsahau tadā|
āhārayetām āhāraṃ sutuṣṭau ca babhūvatuḥ|| 56.62||
tau tu tuṣṭau samālakṣya sarve 'atha śirasā natāḥ|
ūcuḥ prayatnato vākyam aikamatyena te tadā|| 56.63||
pitarau parinirviṇṇā vayam etena janmanā|
icchāmastat parityaktuṃ tannaḥ saṃmantum arhathaḥ|| 56.64||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā pitā tānidam abravīt|
pariṣvajya sutān sarvān bāṣpaparyākulekṣaṇaḥ|| 56.65||
aham āsaṃ purā putrā brāhmaṇaḥ śaṃsitavrataḥ|
divodāsasya rājarṣeḥ sakhā paramasaṃmataḥ|| 56.66||
sa kadācidvane ramye dhanuṣā kurute bhṛśam|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 56.67||
yogyāt tam aham āhedaṃ na tvaṃ vetsi dhanurnṛpa|
ajānan kim idaṃ kleśaṃ vyartham eva karoṣi ca|| 56.68||
provāca rājā viprāṇāṃ mantrajñānaṃ vidhīyate|
āmantraṇe bhojane ca vācā ca kuśalā dvijāḥ|| 56.69||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
sa mayā hasatā prokta ānayasva dhanurmama|| 56.70||
yāvat kṣipāmi lakṣyāya śaraṃ yatra bravīṣi mām|
sa tathoktastadā mahyaṃ saśaraṃ dhanurarpayat|| 56.71||
tenoktaṃ lakṣyam uddiśya śaraḥ kṣipto mayā tataḥ|
tatrābhavat sthito vipro mṛgacārī dṛḍhavrataḥ|| 56.72||
sa tena viddhastejasvī mamāra sahasaiva ca|
so 'ahaṃ taṃ mṛtam ālakṣya rājñā tena visarjitaḥ|| 56.73||
brahmabadhyābhayādghorāt pitaraṃ paripṛṣṭavān|
provāca na bhayaṃ te 'asti brahmavadhyā kutastava|| 56.74||
jātyantaraśataṃ gatvā dṛṣṭam etat svayambhuvā|
tato 'ahaṃ parayā bhaktyā pitṛśuśrūṣaṇe rataḥ|| 56.75||
anayā bhāryayā sārdhaṃ sthito vai bahulāḥ samāḥ|
sa kadācit pitā cāpi mama kālena saṃyutaḥ|| 56.76||
avatasthe ca tatraiva anayaiva sahānaghāḥ|
atha kālena mahatā gavāhaṃ vinipātitaḥ|| 56.77||
agnisthaṃ cāvarūḍhaiṣā rudantī māṃ śubhekṣaṇā|
so 'ahaṃ gavā hataśceti mṛgacārivadhena ca|| 56.78||
vyādhajanmani vipratvādbhraṣṭaḥ pāpena jajñivān|
jāto 'asmi janmanāṃ putrāḥ sahasraṃ bhṛśadāruṇam|| 56.79||
pitṛbhaktyā ca hi tayā samyagārādhanena ca|
nānaśanme smṛtiḥ putrā jñānaṃ cāpi pravartate|| 56.80||
jānāmi brāhmaṇān bhraṣṭān sarvān vai gokṛtena vaḥ|
guroścaivānuśāpena bhraṣṭasaṃjñāṃstathaiva ca|| 56.81||
paścāt tadājñayā putrān sarvān vai muktacetasaḥ|
labdhasaṃjñāṃstathā caiva sarvānadya mahābalāḥ|| 56.82||
mātā ceyaṃ hi vo vetti sādhvī nityaṃ pativratā|
yadahaṃ vo bravīmyadya tat kurudhvaṃ mama priyam|| 56.83||
avāpsyatha tataḥ śreyaḥ sarve yūyam atandritāḥ|
anāmayā viśokāśca na ca saṃjñāṃ prahāsyatha|| 56.84||
putrā janmedam antyaṃ me manuṣyeṣu na saṃśayaḥ|
ito mṛtena gantavyaṃ mayā brahmasadaḥ śubham|| 56.85||
te yūyaṃ māṃ pratīkṣadhvaṃ kaṃcit kālam atandritāḥ|
svargate mayi yacchreyastat kariṣyatha mā śucaḥ|| 56.86||
avaśyaṃ ca sutairmātā pitā caiva suduḥkhitau |
śuśrūṣitavyau nānyo 'asti dharmo 'asmādbalavattaraḥ|| 56.87||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste vismitā bhūtvā naṣṭaśokā vimatsarāḥ|
taṃ kālaṃ paryupāsanta yāvat tau jahatustvasūn|| 56.88||
tayoratītayoḥ samyak kṛtvā te hyaurdhvadehikam|
daśārṇāyāṃ mahānadyāṃ vidhinānaśanena ha|| 56.89||
asādhayanta ātmānaṃ vyādhāḥ saptāpi te tadā|
kālañjare girau bhūyo mṛgāḥ saptaiva jajñire|| 56.90||
smarantastatra te jātiṃ marutprapatanena ha|
sādhayitvā tadātmānaṃ cakravākeṣu jajñire|| 56.91||
mṛgatve yāni nāmāni teṣāṃ tāni nibodha me|
dīrghajīvo hyanādhṛṣṭo vāyuvego 'abhikampanaḥ|| 56.92||
śrīpārśvaḥ śaṅkhapāccaiva somalakṣyaśca saptamaḥ|
jātiṃ smarantaste pūrvām anyonyam abhimānya ca|| 56.93||
sahitāḥ sahasā prāṇān marutprapatanājjahuḥ|
te saptasaṃkhyā vyādheṣu mṛgeṣu ca tathā punaḥ|| 56.94||
janma prāpya puno jātāḥ śaradvīpe khagāstataḥ|
śaradvīpam iti khyātaṃ kāmpilyeṣu saraḥ śubham|| 56.95||
tatrāpi cakravākāste saptājāyanta sodarāḥ|
maruddevaḥ śikhaṇḍī ca rathanemisvarastathā|
śikhī jīvo 'atha vṛkṣaśca dhvaja ityeva te smṛtāḥ|| 56.96||
teṣāṃ tatropapannānāṃ kadācidaṇuhaḥ svayam|
kāmpilyako mahātejā rājā taṃ deśam āgamat|| 56.97||
sa tat saraḥ samāsādya strībhiḥ saha mudānvitaḥ|
reme mandākinīṃ prāpya apsarobhirivāmaraḥ|| 56.98||
taṃ krīḍamānaṃ saṃdṛśya maruddevasya tatra vai|
cakravākasya tasyāsīt spṛhā tān viṣayān prati|| 56.99||
yadyasyāhaṃ sutaḥ syāṃ vai prāpnuyāṃ rājyam eva ca|
tato 'ahaṃ viṣayānetān prāpnuyāṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 56.100||
tasya taccintitaṃ jñātvā dvitīyaścakrasāhvayaḥ|
śikhaṇḍīti samākhyātaḥ sa tam āha tadā hasan|| 56.101||
bhavatā rājaputratvaṃ rājyaṃ caiva vicintitam|
tatrāhaṃ te purodhāḥ syāṃ mamāpyeṣa manorathaḥ|| 56.102||
tābhyāṃ taccintitaṃ jñātvā rathanemisvarastataḥ|
acintayata tatrāhaṃ sacivaḥ syāṃ tava prabho|| 56.103||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tathā cintayatāṃ trayāṇām itare tataḥ|
cakrāhvayāstadā kruddhā idaṃ tānabruvan vacaḥ|| 56.104||
acintanīyaṃ yuṣmābhiścintitaṃ viṣayārthibhiḥ|
tasmādyūyam ito muktā avāpsyatha manoratham|| 56.105||
tāñchaptvā dīnamanasaḥ samālakṣya punaśca te|
tena tadrājaputratvaṃ cintitaṃ rājyam eva ca|| 56.106||
kṛpayā tam idaṃ vākyam abruvan naṣṭacetasam|
bahusāntvaguṇopetaṃ svayaṃ duḥkhitavadyathā|| 56.107||
vayaṃ tava prabhāveṇa tīrṇāḥ kṛcchram idaṃ prabho|
bhavān matiprado 'asmākaṃ setubhūto mato hi naḥ|| 56.108||
bhavān yadi hi na brūyāt pitR̥ṇāṃ gaurnivedyatām|
śuśrūṣemaśca na pitR̥n na sam saṃjñāṃ tatas bhavet|| 56.109||
tava prabhāvādetanno yogaiśvaryapravartanam|
tato vayaṃ punaḥ śreyastava brūmaḥ śṛṇuṣva naḥ|| 56.110||
tāvat tvaṃ saktahṛdayo bhaviṣyasi narādhipaḥ|
yāvadasmadvacastathyaṃ na śroṣyasi sahāyavān|
yogajñānam avāpyaiva prāpsyase ca gatiṃ śubhām|| 56.111||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste sahitāḥ sarve yuktāmāno mahākhagāḥ|
khagatvaṃ samparityajya yonim anyāṃ prapedire|| 56.112||
sarve tataste munikopadagdhā vyādhā mṛgāścakrasamāhvayāśca|
jātāḥ puno mānuṣavigraheṣu yogeśvarāste traya eva rājye|| 56.113||
iti skandapurāṇe saptavyādhopakhyāne
kauśikaśāpe ṣaṭpañcāśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 56.56||

saptapañcāśo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
catvāraste tu śāstāraḥ khagāḥ svacchandataḥ punaḥ|
yāyāvarasya viprasya sutā jātā mahātmanaḥ|| 57.1||
teṣu jāteṣu vipro 'asāvakleśena mahātapāḥ|
vṛttiṃ samānayāmāsa teṣāṃ bhāgyapuraḥsaraḥ|| 57.2||
cīrṇavedavratāste tu vedān sāṅgānadhītya ca|
yogam eva nyaṣevanta tanniṣṭhāstatparāyaṇāḥ|| 57.3||
itare 'api trayo vyāsa karmaṇā svena coditāḥ|
pratyapadyanta tajjanma yat purā tairvicintitam|| 57.4||
prathamo hyaṇuhājjajñe brahmadatta iti smṛtaḥ|
eko 'aṇuhasya putro 'abhūddvitīyastatpurodhasaḥ|| 57.5||
tṛtīyaḥ sacivasyātha trayaste janma tadgatāḥ|
trayo 'agnaya ivāsaṃste lokāstraya ivāthavā|
avarddhanta mahātmānastrayaste sāgarā iva|| 57.6||
teṣām avāptavidyānāṃ yogyānāṃ ca svakarmaṇi|
pitaraḥ svāni karmāṇi pradadurhṛṣṭamānasāḥ|| 57.7||
aṇuhaḥ pradadau rājyaṃ brahmadattāya puṣkalam|
kīrtimatyā ca sahitastato vanam agācca saḥ|| 57.8||
purodhā dhṛtarātastu putraṃ sve karmaṇi prabhuḥ|
sthāpayitvā jagāmātha paṃcālaṃ śaṃsitavrataḥ|| 57.9||
sacivo 'api sudhanvā tu brahmadhanvānam acyutam|
putraṃ sve karmaṇi sthāpya jagāma saha bhāryayā|| 57.10||
gateṣu teṣu svā/llokān brahamdattaḥ pratāpavān|
pañcālabrahmadhanvabhyāṃ saha rājyaṃ cakāra ha|| 57.11||
praśāsatastathā rājyaṃ yajato bhuñjataśca ha|
jagmuḥ sukhena bahulāḥ samāḥ sukṛtinastadā|| 57.12||
atha kālena mahatā sabhāryaḥ sasuhṛjjanaḥ|
tasthau sa veśmani sukhaṃ kubera iva puṣpake|| 57.13||
tataḥ sarvarutajñātā pipīlaṃ kāmakāraṇāt|
pipīlikāyāṃ cātūṇi kurvāṇaṃ so 'anvapaśyata|| 57.14||
sa tu jñānādviniścintya kṛmiyonāvapīdṛśam|
vivṛtaṃ śabdavaccaiva hāsam utsṛjatānaghaḥ|| 57.15||
tat tasya hasitaṃ dṛṣṭvā patnī nīlotpalekṣaṇā|
cukopa kim idaṃ me 'adya vikṛtaṃ lakṣitaṃ tvayā|| 57.16||
tāṃ sa rājā samāvgnaḥ priyāṃ prāṇairgarīyasīm|
prasādayan na caivāsya prasīdata śubhānanā|| 57.17||
sā yadā bahu tathyaṃ ca ucyamānā na tuṣyati|
tadā tasyāḥ prasādārthe sa viṣṇuṃ samprasādayat|| 57.18||
devaṃ sālavanaṃ gatvā pañcālena sahaiva saḥ|
brahmadhanvapurovāho rathena mahatā mahān|| 57.19||
tatrāsau saptame tvahni viṣṇunābhivisarjitaḥ|
jagāma naraśārdūlaḥ kāmpilyaṃ svaṃ purottamam|| 57.20||
etasminneva kāle tu catvāro brāhmaṇāḥ śubhāḥ|
yogena mahatā yuktā idam ūcuḥ parasparam|| 57.21||
vayaṃ kṛtārthāḥ kiṃ kāryam iha tiṣṭhāma mānuṣe|
gacchāma brahmayoniṃ svāṃ mucyāmo 'asmān mahābhayāt|| 57.22||
avasīdanti te caiva trayo 'asmākaṃ sahavratāḥ|
bodhayāmahe tāṃścaiva yathā neyuḥ parābhavam|| 57.23||
tataste pitaraṃ sarve praṇamyocurdvijātayaḥ|
vayaṃ yogeśvarāstāta siddhā vai svena karmaṇā|| 57.24||
āpṛcchāmo gamiṣyāmaḥ svāṃ yoniṃ brahmanirmitām|
tyaktvemān mānuṣān dehān visarjaya namastava|| 57.25||
pitovāca|
putrānicchanti pitarastārayiṣyanti no bhayāt|
bhayaṃ taccaihikaputrāḥ paratra ca durāsadam|| 57.26||
te yūyam ṛṇasaṃyuktā amuktvā svaṃ nibandhanam|
kathaṃ gacchatha bhadraṃ vo nādharmaṃ paripaśyatha|| 57.27||
sūta ūcuḥ|
vayaṃ yogeśvarāstāta lokāṃstubhyam anāmayān|| 57.28||
asmābhistvaṃ kathaṃ putrairbrahmatvaṃ nāpnuyāḥ pitaḥ|
ihāpi loke dravyaṃ te vidhāsyāmastathā śṛṇu|| 57.29||
idaṃ tvaṃ patram ādāya brahmadattasya darśaya|
sa vācayanneva nṛpo vṛttiṃ te saṃvidhāsyati|| 57.30||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
prabhāvajñastatasteṣāṃ pitā sa munipuṅgava|
mene tadvai tathā sarvam anumene ca tān punaḥ|| 57.31||
athāsanāni baddhvā te yuktā jagmustapodhanāḥ|
jyotirbhūtānapaśyacca pitā teṣām atidyutiḥ|| 57.32||
sa tu lekhaṃ samādaya putrān svānabhicintayan|
kāmpilyam agamat tūrṇaṃ didṛkṣurnṛpasattamam|| 57.33||
sa ca rājā sālavanādāgataḥ prāviśat puram|
brāhmaṇo dūrataścāsya taṃ lekhaṃ samadarśayat|| 57.34||
nimitāni ca saṃlakṣya śubhāni ca narādhipaḥ|
lekham ānayatetyuktvā dhārayāmāsa taṃ ratham|| 57.35||
sa puradvārasaṃsthastu rathena mahata tadā|
brahmadhanvadhṛtacchatraḥ pañcālāvījitānanaḥ|| 57.36||
gṛhītvā lekham avyagram avācayata taṃ tadā|
ślokadvayaṃ cāpyabhavat tasmi/llekhe śubhapradam|| 57.37||
ye te gurukṛtācchāpādgovadhenāvapīḍitāḥ|
pitṛbhaktyā kṛtajñānā jātāḥ sarve śubhodayāḥ|| 57.38||
sapta vyādhā daśārṇeṣu mṛgāḥ kālañjare girau|
cakravākāḥ śaradvīpe haṃsāḥ sarasi mānase|| 57.39||
te 'api jātāḥ kurukṣetre brāhmaṇā vedapāragāḥ|
prasthitā dīrgham adhvānaṃ yūyaṃ kim avasīdatha|| 57.40||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ślokadvayaṃ tathā śrutvā trayaste viṣapītavat|
mohaṃ tadā tu samprāpya labdhasaṃjñā viśan puram|| 57.41||
te praviśya puraṃ caiva veśma caivāpyatandraitāḥ|
iti ceti ca saṃcintya vanāya dadhire manaḥ|| 57.42||
sā ca patnī mahābhāgā abhigamya narādhipam|
idam āha mudā yuktā rājānaṃ sasuhṛjjanam|| 57.43||
bhavān yogeśvaro bhūtvā sakto bhogeṣu sarvaśaḥ|
prabodhārthaṃ tato 'ahaṃ te krodham āhārayantadā|| 57.44||
jānāmi tvāṃ rutajñaṃ ca jānāmi tvāṃ khagaṃ tathā|
ato 'ahaṃ jānatī rājan pratobodhārtham udayatā|| 57.45||
tasmādvipram imaṃ caiva teṣāṃ pitaram avyayam|
dhanena yojayasvādya putraṃ rājye 'abhiṣicya ca|| 57.46||
śvo gacchāva vanaṃ rājan mā kālaṃ pratipālaya|
rājā tat kṛtyam akhilaṃ kṛtvā patnyā sahavrataḥ|| 57.47||
jagāma vanam uddiśya yogena ca divaṃ yayau|
paṃcālo 'api gate tasmiṃstapaḥ kṛtvā suduścaram|| 57.48||
cakāra pāraṇaṃ caiva yakṣatvaṃ cāpyavāpa ha|
brahmadhanvā ca kālena sumahātmā dṛḍhavrataḥ|| 57.49||
himavattanayāṃ devīṃ tapasā samapaśyata|
varadāṃ tāṃ tadā dṛṣṭvā brahmadhanvābravīcchubhām|| 57.50||
icchāmi kāmarūpitvaṃ tvadbhaktiṃ caiva nityadā|
kṛcchraṃ mahacca prāptasya tvayaivoddharaṇaṃ tataḥ|| 57.51||
evam astviti sā coktvā jagāmeṣṭāṃ gatiṃ tadā|
brahmadhanvāpi matto 'abhūnmadanena durātmavān|| 57.52||
sa bhūtvā dhārmikaḥ pūrvam adharmeṇābhipīḍitaḥ|
abhimene sa kanyāśca ṛṣīpatnīśca sarvaśaḥ|| 57.53||
bhartṛrūpeṇa gatvā ca kāmena sa vimohitaḥ|
na ca kaścidvijānāti tathā vartantam antaśaḥ|| 57.54||
atha hāla iti khyāto mṛgacārī mahātapāḥ|
tasya patnī sudharmābhūnnāmnā rūpavatī dṛḍham|| 57.55||
kathayanti hi tāṃ devāḥ siddhāśca saha cāraṇaiḥ|
asamā rūpato 'anyābhistriṣu lokeṣu bhāminī|| 57.56||
na ca tasya sabhāryasya antaraṃ sa bubodha ha|
kasmin kāle bhavet tasyā virahaḥ patinā saha|| 57.57||
sa brahmadhanvā tāṃ śrutvā tathā rūpavatīṃ satīm|
patyāsyā virahākāṃkṣī vyāghrarūpaṃ cakāra ha|| 57.58||
kṛtvā ca sumahadrūpaṃ vikṛtaṃ bhairavaṃ tadā|
atrasayanmṛgān vyāsa darśanena subāliśaḥ|| 57.59||
tadvyāghrabhayasaṃtrastamṛgayūthaṃ tadā vibho|
manonilajavavyagram adṛśyaṃ samprapadyata|| 57.60||
mṛgaiḥ saha ca hālo 'api jīvitaiṣi tadā gataḥ|
sudharmā brāhmaṇī sāpi bhayādvyāghrasya bhāminī|| 57.61||
strīsvabhāvācca patitā nānvagacchanmṛgavrajam|
ekākinīṃ ca tāṃ dṛṣṭvā brahmadhanvā durātmavān|| 57.62||
vyāghrarūpaṃ samutsṛjya tām idaṃ pratyabhāṣata|
mṛdunā sāntvayuktena vacasā bhayapīḍitām|| 57.63||
mā bhīrbhavatu te bhadre patiste 'ahaṃ sumadhyame|
mṛgarājo gato 'asau ca samāśvasa mama priye|| 57.64||
taṃ samāśvasya sāpaśyat patirūpaṃ mahayaśā|
hṛdā cācintayaddṛṣṭo mayāsau tairmṛgaiḥ saha|| 57.65||
jīvitaiṣī palāyan vai kuto 'ayaṃ puna āgataḥ|
devendro māṃ durācāraḥ sadā dharṣatyatandritaḥ|| 57.66||
so 'ayaṃ kāmayituṃ prāptaḥ kiṃ na syādantaraiṣivān|
tasmāddrakṣyāmyahaṃ samyag draṣṭuṃ divyena cakṣuṣā|| 57.67||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
etasminnantare so 'atha brahmadhanvā kare 'agrahīt|
tām idaṃ cocivān hṛṣṭaḥ kiṃ tvaṃ cintayase hṛdā|| 57.68||
na mām āliṅgase 'adya tvaṃ mṛtyorāsyādvinirgatam|
nanu te 'ahaṃ priyo bhartā mā krudho varavarṇini|| 57.69||
tatastāṃ sa tadā dauṣṭyāt kapole samajighrata|
pariṣvajya ca durātmā gātrairgātrāṇyapīḍayat|| 57.70||
nīvīṃ vyasraṃsayaccaiva adharaṃ cāpibadbalāt|
bubudhe sā ca taṃ duṣṭaṃ karmaṇā tena śobhanā|| 57.71||
sudharmovāca|
na tvaṃ mama patirmūḍha śakrastvaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ|
na bhūyo madanasyāsmi viṣayo 'ahaṃ sudurmate|| 57.72||
sa tayāpyevam uktastu avadhūtaśca sarvaśaḥ|
papāta dharaṇīpṛṣṭhe svaṃ ca rūpaṃ prapadyata|| 57.73||
tataḥ sā krodhatāmrākṣī dhakṣyamāṇeva cakṣuṣā|
nirīkṣya vadanaṃ subhūridaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 57.74||
ṛṣipatnyastvayā bahvyo vyaṃsitā duṣṭacetasā|
na mādṛśī tvayā kācidanyā hyasādita purā|| 57.75||
idānīṃ karmaṇastasya pūrvam ācaritasya te|
phalaṃ prāptam idaṃ paśya matsakāśāddurāsadam|| 57.76||
yadeva rūpaṃ kṛtvā tvaṃ mṛgānatrāsayo balāt|
vicariṣyasi tenaiva rūpeṇa bahulāḥ samāḥ|| 57.77||
aśaktaścāpi hantuṃ tvaṃ bhavitā mānuṣaṃ kvacit|
ṣaṣṭhe ca kāle samprāpte mṛgaṃ bhakṣyam avāpsyasi|| 57.78||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
abhivyāhṛtya taṃ krūraṃ śubhācārā manasvinī|
jagāma tān mṛgāṃstveva tataḥ patim apaśyata|| 57.79||
so 'api duḥkhena santapto manvānastāṃ hateti ca|
vilapanneva tāṃ dṛṣṭvā pariṣvajyedam abravīt|| 57.80||
diṣṭyā tvam asi samprāptā mṛtyorāsyādviniḥsṛtā|
kaccinna tena dṛṣṭāsi mṛgarājena śobhane|| 57.81||
sudharmovāca|
nāsau mṛgendro durbuddhiḥ ko 'apyasau kāmarūpavān|
madarthaṃ samanuprāpto mayā dagdhaḥ pataṅgavat|| 57.82||
sa śāpānmama duṣṭātmā śārdūlaprakṛtiṃ gataḥ|
rājeva śaktiśāpena saudāso rākṣasīṃ tanum|| 57.83||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyāstadvacanaṃ śrutvā hālo dharmārthatattvavit|
divyena cakṣuṣāpaśyadbrahmadhanvānam avyayam|| 57.84||
tām uvāca satīṃ bhāryām idaṃ sa karuṇātmakaḥ|
kṛtaṃ duṣṭaṃ tvayātreyi sadbhiḥ karma vigarhitam|| 57.85||
mahatastapasaste 'adya kṣayo 'ayaṃ sumahān kṛtaḥ|
na duṣyanti striyaḥ sādhvi nadyo yadvadvigāhanaiḥ|| 57.86||
na caiva śakyaṃ dharmeṇa saṃguptāṃ tvāṃ pramarditum|
yathā viṣeṇa saṃcchannam annaṃ bhoktuṃ hi mānavaiḥ|| 57.87||
atra te vartayiṣyāmi purāvṛttaṃ mahātape|
yat pativratayā pūrvaṃ kṛtaṃ dīptena tejasā|| 57.88||
āsīdbhalandano nāma ṛṣiḥ paramadhārmikaḥ|
vidvāṃścaiva dayāvāṃśca pṛthivīvadvyavasthitaḥ|| 57.89||
ṛgnāmnī tasya bhāryābhūdvāsiṣṭhī puṇyalakṣaṇā|
rūpeṇāpratimā sādhvī na tasyāḥ strīḥ samā kvacit|| 57.90||
pativratā mahābhāgā sarvadharmaviduttamā|
tasyāḥ patim ṛte nānyaddaivataṃ bhuvi vidyate|| 57.91||
apaśyanta kadācidvai devāstāṃ kamalekṣaṇām|
tasyā rūpaguṇonmattā lebhurna dhṛtim ekaśaḥ|| 57.92||
na śakyate ca sā prāptuṃ na dūtībhirna karmaṇā|
na dānena na saṃmānairna balena na sevayā|| 57.93||
vahnistām agnyagārasthāṃ praviṣṭām agrahīcchubhām|
na cāpi sāham asmīti na ca nāsmītyathābravīt|| 57.94||
na krodho nāpi darpo 'asyā na māno na ca matsaraḥ|
tasyāḥ priyam abhūnnānyat patim evānvacintayat|| 57.95||
vibhāvasurapi vyaktam iyaṃ mām icchatīti ha|
abhyupetya na duṣṭeti bhāvena surasattamaḥ|| 57.96||
atha hitvā svakaṃ deham adehaḥ samapadyata|
evaṃ vai bhāskaro vāyurvaruṇaścandra eva ca|| 57.97||
sarve videhāḥ saṃvṛttāstatastāṃ samprasādayan|
sāpi tān nāvadat kiṃcit puruṣānaghaśaṅkayā|| 57.98||
bhartuścākathayat sarvaṃ sa tānidam uvāca ha|
iyaṃ patnī mahābhāgā mama sarvāṅgasundarī|| 57.99||
neyaṃ kupyati yuṣmākaṃ jāne hyasyā vrataṃ śubham|
matto 'api vo bhayaṃ nāsti nāhaṃ kupye kathaṃcana|| 57.100||
matprasādādvidehāpi dehavanto bhaviṣyatha|
tataste dehavanto vai tuṣṭuvustaṃ bhalandanam|| 57.101||
ūcurvaraṃ vṛṇīṣvādya tuṣṭāḥ smastava sarvathā|
sovāca rajasā nāryaḥ śuddhyantu madanugrahāt|| 57.102||
karmaṇā ca vimucyantāṃ vyavahāryā bhavantu ca|
sarvaśaucā bhaveyuśca aduṣṭāḥ sarvakarmasu|| 57.103||
hala uvāca|
tataste taṃ namaskṛtya sabhāryaṃ brahmavādinam|
jagmurdevāḥ praśaṃsantaḥ sarve vahnipurogamāḥ|| 57.104||
evaṃ tvam api dharmajñe nityaṃ patim anuvratā|
kastvāṃ samartho devo 'api spraṣṭum anye kuto janāḥ|| 57.105||
tīrthabhūtāḥ striyaścāpi na duṣyanti kathaṃcana|
madrūpaṃ kṛtavān yasmāt tasmācchāpaṃ na cārhati|| 57.106||
tasmāt kariṣye tasyāham adṛṣṭasyāpi śobhane|
anugrahaṃ dharmayuktaṃ yena śreyo hyavāpsyati|| 57.107||
vyāghrasyāpi priye tasya smṛtirnityaṃ bhaviṣyati|
sarvakāryeṣu dharmeṣu dharmeṇa ca caiṣyati|| 57.108||
yato 'asya kāmarūpitvaṃ yena mattaḥ sadā hyabhūt|
tata eva punaḥ śreyaḥ prāpsyate madanugrahāt|| 57.109||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa eva vyāsa duṣṭātmā viśvāmitrāśrame rataḥ|
agrāraṇye sadā hi āsīddevyā gaṇapatiḥ kṛtaḥ|| 57.110||
ya idaṃ tasya māhātmyaṃ dhārayecchrāvayīta vai|
satataṃ brāhmaṇaṃ vyāsa yogaiśvaryam avāpnuyāt|| 57.111||
yogeśvaratvaṃ kāṅkṣadbhiretadadhyeyam antaśaḥ|
janmāntaraṃ samāsādya prāpnuvanti na saṃśayaḥ|| 57.112||
śṛṇuyādya imaṃ satataṃ prayataḥ śucirekamanā manujaḥ|
priyavatsa hi śakrasamānavapuḥ sukṛtena kṛtena pumān|| 57.113||
iti skandapurāṇe
saptapañcāśo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 57.57||

aṣṭapañcāśattamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
varān gṛhītvā rudrāṇī tasmiñchikharisattame|
akarot kim iti brūhi sarvaṃ devyā viceṣṭitam|| 58.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
svayambhuvi gate devī tapaso virarāma ha|
sā tuṣṭā varalābhena cintayantī tadā varam|| 58.2||
nyavaikṣata diśaḥ sarvāḥ prasannavadanekṣaṇā|
kasyaitat kathayāmīti devaṃ hitveti cābravīt|| 58.3||
śāstrajñaṃ kaṃciduddiśya yathārthaṃ śāstracintakaḥ|
putralambhakṛtaṃ harṣaṃ cintayantyā muhurmuhuḥ|| 58.4||
apatajjalam atyarthaśītalaṃ susugandhi ca|
bahvabhūt sarasi svacchaṃ tasyāstat tejasā jalam|| 58.5||
śiṣye buddhiguṇeneva guruṇā jñānam āhitam|
vigāhamānā sā devī tat saro vimalodakam|| 58.6||
reje viyanmadhyagatā dīpteva savituḥ prabhā|
vigāhamānā vyajahat kṛṣṇāṃ kośīṃ tadānaghā|| 58.7||
sā vireje tayā muktā kalevendorghanātyaye|
tasyāḥ kośyāḥ samabhavat kauśikī lokaviśrutā|
viśvaṃ sisṛkṣato dhāturdehādiva purā niśā|| 58.8||
bimbādharā tīkṣṇasucārudaṃṣṭrā prasannatārādhipacāruvaktrā|
sujātanīlāṃcitadīrghakeśī kiṃcitsamabhyunnataromarājī|| 58.9||
susaṃsthitābhyāṃ caraṇāmbujābhyāṃ pradakṣiṇāvartanimagnanābhiḥ|
vigūḍhajānvasthiśirā sugulphā vinākṛtevāmburuheṇa lakṣṃīḥ|| 58.10||
prasannarūpā prathamodgatastanī praphullanīlāmbujacārulocanā|
susaṃskṛtairvajramaṇipravekibhirvibhūṣitā cābharaṇaiḥ sumadhyamā|| 58.11||
sāṅgasā bādhakeyūrā kaṭakodbhāsitatviṣā|
bibharti sā bhujānaṣṭau sāyudhānaparājitā|| 58.12||
bādhagodhāṅgulitrāṇā kavacaṃ bibhratī śubham|
durbhedyaṃ sahajaṃ bhāsvat sendrairapi surāsuraiḥ|| 58.13||
nibaddhatūṇīrayugā pragṛhītaśarāsanā|
vasānā padmakiñjalkarucire vāsasī tadā|| 58.14||
jānubhyām avaniṃ gatvā śirasi ādhāya cāñjalim|
vyajñāpayata sā devī brūhi kiṃ karavāṇi te|| 58.15||
mūrdhnyupāghrāya tāṃ devīṃ pariṣvajya ca pīḍitam|
bhavānī prāha saṃhṛṣṭā mūrtisthānaṃ mamāvyaye|| 58.16||
jarāmaraṇahīnā tvaṃ śokaduḥkhavivarjitā|
bhaviṣyati mahāyogā saṃyugeṣvaparājitā|| 58.17||
kauśikīti ca nāmnā tvaṃ loke khyātiṃ gamiṣyati|
anyaiśca nāmabhiḥ ślāghyairguṇakarmābhisaṃśrayaiḥ|| 58.18||
tava bhaktāḥ smariṣyanti yeti durgeṣu saṃsthitāḥ|
durgāṇi te tariṣyanti tvatprasādādvarānane|| 58.19||
varā vareṇyā varadā durgā sarvārthasādhanī|
itthaṃ tvāṃ nāmabhirdivyaiḥ stoṣyanti munayaḥ sadā|| 58.20||
jāpaiḥ praṇatibhirhomabhirupahāraiḥ pṛthagvidhaiḥ|
prāṇinaḥ pūjayiṣyanti bhavatīṃ bhuvi sarvadā|| 58.21||
siṃhayuktaṃ tato devī ratham ādityavarcasam|
sasarja sapatākaṃ ca kiṃkiṇījālamaṇḍitam|
vindhyaṃ girivaraṃ cāsyā nivāsāya samādiśat|| 58.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
saivam uktā tadā devī praṇamya bhuvaneśvarīm|
āruroha rathaṃ divyaṃ kārtasvaramayaṃ śubham|| 58.23||
vyomagena rathenātha nānāratnāṃśumālinā|
jagāmāśu tato vindhyaṃ nānādrumalatānvitam|| 58.24||
vihaṅgamarutairvindhyaḥ svāgateneva kauśikīm|
apūjayadameyāṃ tāṃ tatra prāptāṃ tadānaghām|| 58.25||
vāribhirvimalaiḥ śītairnirjharodaraniḥsṛtaiḥ|
sa puṣpanikaraiḥ puṇyairarghaṃ cāsyai dadanniva|| 58.26||
atha mṛgapatināgaṃ trastaparyantanāgaṃ cakitahariṇayūthakṣuṇṇadarbhāṅkurāgram|
varamahiṣaviṣāṇacchinnagulmāvatānaṃ girivaram atiramyaṃ kauśikī sābhyapaśyat|| 58.27||
vyarocayata sā devī vāsāya śikharaṃ gireḥ|
utphullapādapālīnavihaṅgagaṇanāditam|| 58.28||
nirjharodakasaṃparkaharitopalaśādvalam|
nānādrumalatāpuṣpasurabhīkṛtamārutam|| 58.29||
tuhinanikaraśītairnirjharāmbupravāhairnicitapṛthunitambottuṅgaparyantasānum|
girivaraśikharaṃ tat sādhyuvāsātha devī kusumitataruśākhāśliṣṭamattadvirepham|| 58.30||
ya idaṃ paṭhate nityaṃ śṛṇuyādvā samāhitaḥ|
kauśikyāḥ sambhavaṃ samyak sa yāti paramāṃ gatim|| 58.31||
iti skandapurāṇe kauśikīsambhavo nāma
aṣṭapañcāśattamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 58.58||

ūnaṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastāṃ kauśikīṃ tatra prasthāpya himavatsutā|
vireme tapasastīvrāt sasnau ca vidhivat tadā|| 59.1||
vasānā vāsasī śukle divyasraganulepanā|
pārśvasthaṃ parvataṃ vīkṣya provāca varadāsmi te|| 59.2||
evam uktavatīṃ devīṃ śikharī mūrtimāṃstadā|
praṇipatya varaṃ vavre mayi sānnidhyam astu te|| 59.3||
nāma caiva mama khyātiṃ tava nāmābhilakṣitam|
yātu lokeṣu sarveṣu tvatprasādānmaheśvari|| 59.4||
agniśca varadāṃ vavre mā gāḥ kopaṃ mayīśvari|
sadā puṣphaphalatvaṃ ca vṛkṣāstāṃ tatra vavrire|| 59.5||
suprasannā bhavāsmākaṃ tvayi bhaktiśca no 'astviti|
tatastāṃ vavrire devīṃ sarvāśca paricārikāḥ|| 59.6||
upāsyamānā bahvībhirdevatābhirgirīndrajā|
abhibhūyānyatejāṃsi bhānavīva nabhau prabhā|| 59.7||
hṛdaye 'api sthitā patyuḥ patyau hṛdayasaṃsthite|
sā vai girīndratanayā viyuktāsmītyamanyata|| 59.8||
atha sā tejasāṃ dhāma patiṃ sarvajagatpatim|
varadā varadaṃ draṣṭuṃ gamanāyopacakrame|| 59.9||
namaskṛtā tadvanadevatābhiḥ pradakṣiṇīkṛtya samiddham agnim|
ṛṣīṃstato vandyatamābhivandya janaṃ ca teṣāṃ pratipūjya pūjyam|| 59.10||
utpapāta tato vyoma sā sārdhaṃ somanandinā|
siṃhena ca jagaddhātrī gaṇaiḥ parijanena ca|| 59.11||
viyati jaladavṛndān vikṣipantī svadhāmnā
himajalakaṇsaśītairvījyamānā marudbhiḥ|
girivaratanayā sā patyureva smarantī
madanadahanamūrterāśu pārśvaṃ jagāma|| 59.12||
iti skandapurāṇe
ūnaṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 59.59||

ṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
athāsau brahmaṇaḥ putraṃ vyāsaḥ prāha kṛtāñjaliḥ|
kimarthaṃ kauśikī vindhyaṃ devyā sampreṣitā tadā|| 60.1||
evam uktastadā dhīmān vyāsena brahmaṇaḥ sutaḥ|
yathāvṛttaṃ purā sarvam ākhyātum upacakrame|| 60.2||
ārirādhayiṣurdevīṃ vindhyastepe purā tapaḥ|
tatastuṣṭābravīdvindhyaṃ pārvatī varadāsmi te|| 60.3||
mayi vāso 'astu te nityam evam ādityarodhanaḥ|
vavre girīndratanayāṃ prāha sā ca tathāstviti|| 60.4||
svatanuṃ sā dvidhābhūtām agnerdīptāṃ śikhām iva|
dāhāya dānavendrāṇāṃ prāhiṇot kauśikīm ataḥ|| 60.5||
atha taṃ brahmaṇaḥ sūnum uvāca munisattamaḥ|
girirvindhyo mahāprajña katham ādityarodhanaḥ|| 60.6||
sanatkumāraḥ provāca pṛṣṭo vyāsena dhīmatā|
śṛṇu yasmādabhūdvindhyo girirādityarodhanaḥ|| 60.7||
purā vindhyo 'abravīt sūryaṃ kasmāt tvaṃ na karoṣi mām|
pradakṣiṇaṃ yathā meruṃ kā te 'avajñā mayi prabho|| 60.8||
pratyākhyātaḥ sa sūryeṇa vindhyo giriravardhata|
ruddhvā tasya sthito mārgaṃ tasmādādityarodhanaḥ|| 60.9||
naṣṭāloke tato loke devāḥ saṃvignacetasaḥ|
agastyam upasaṃgamya vākyam ūcuḥ samāhitāḥ|| 60.10||
saviturmārgam āvṛtya girirvindhyo vyavasthitaḥ|
taṃ vāraya mahāprājña gatirnaḥ sarvadā bhavān|| 60.11||
tam agastyo giriṃ gatvā provācetthaṃ mahātapāḥ|
yāsyāmi dakṣiṇām āśāṃ panthānaṃ dehi parvata|| 60.12||
yāvat pratinivarteyaṃ tāvacca sthātum arhasi|
tataḥ prabhṛti caiveha nābhūdāgamanaṃ muneḥ|| 60.13||
atha papraccha taṃ vyāsaḥ pitāmahasutaṃ prabhum|
kauśikī prahitā vindhyaṃ dānavānāṃ vināśane|| 60.14||
ke te kasya kimarthaṃ vā kauśikyā dānavā hatāḥ|
etat sarvaṃ samāsena praśnaṃ me vaktum arhasi|| 60.15||
pitāmahasuto dhīmān vyāsenaivaṃ pracoditaḥ|
praśnam etaṃ samāsena vyākhyātum upacakrame|| 60.16||
devāsure purātīte saṃyuge paramādbhute|
sundo nisundaśca sutau nisumbhasya babhūvatuḥ|| 60.17||
hatān niśāmya tau bandhūn suraiḥ sarvān mahāhave
devān prati susaṃkruddhau garjantau govṛṣāviva|| 60.18||
siṃhāviva mahāsattvau hṛtadaṃṣṭrānakhāyudhau|
śvasantau saviṣāvugrau bhagnadaṃṣṭrāvivoragau|| 60.19||
aśaktau tau surairyoddhuṃ hatapakṣau mahāsurau|
suparṇāviva saṃkruddhau chinnapakṣau mahābalau|| 60.20||
tapasi ādhāya tau ceto gokarṇaṃ prati jagmatuḥ|
ārirādhayiṣū devaṃ brahmāṇam amitaujasau|| 60.21||
athovāca tato vyāso gokarṇaṃ kathayasva me|
kasmin deśe kimarthaṃ vā kena votpāditaṃ purā|| 60.22||
provāca brahmaṇaḥ sūnurvyāsenaivaṃ pracoditaḥ|
śṛṇu vatsa samāsena puṇyaṃ gokarṇasambhavam|| 60.23||
hate triśirasi tvaṣṭā putre jyāyasi vajriṇā|
vṛtraṃ nāma punaḥ putramasṛjat tapasāṃ nidhiḥ|| 60.24||
pralambabāhuṃ vṛttāsyaṃ pīnavistīrṇavakṣasam|
suśliṣṭajānuṃ suhanuṃ jaladadhvānanisvanam|| 60.25||
sukṣiptapārśvaṃ sukaṭiṃ dīrgharaktāntalocanam|
samare sarvadevānāṃ jetāram aparājitam|| 60.26||
sa nirjityāmarān sarvāñjagrāsendraṃ mahādyutiḥ|
tato maharṣibhiḥ sṛṣṭā jṛmbhikā taṃ samāviśat|| 60.27||
tasyātha jṛmbhamāṇasya nirjagāma śatakratuḥ|
vadanādāśu saṃkṣipya svāṃ tanuṃ yogamāyayā|| 60.28||
tasya yogabalaṃ dṛṣṭvā vīryaṃ śauryaṃ ca saṃyuge|
tato bhītāḥ surāḥ sarve brahmāṇaṃ śaraṇaṃ yayuḥ|| 60.29||
tān dṛṣṭvā sa tadā bhītānamarānamaradviṣaḥ|
provācāsau prajeśānaḥ padmayoniḥ pitāmahaḥ|| 60.30||
parājitān vo jānāmi vṛtreṇa raṇamūrdhani|
upāyaṃ taṃ na paśyāmi yenāsau jīyate yudhi|| 60.31||
yāsyāma sahitāḥ sarve devaṃ draṣṭum umāpatim|
viśveśvaraṃ vidhātāraṃ varadaṃ bhaktavatsalam|| 60.32||
sa naḥ praṇāmairbhaktyā ca stutyā cārādhitaḥ prabhuḥ|
mahādevo mahāyogī śambhuḥ śāntiṃ vidhāsyati|| 60.33||
athottasthuḥ surāḥ sarve devadevaṃ didṛkṣavaḥ|
apaśyanto viceruśca mahīṃ sodadhiparvatām|| 60.34||
atha viṣṇurmahāyogī devīṃ himavataḥ sutām|
apaśyat pāṃsudigdhāṅgīm āsīnāṃ bālarūpiṇīm|| 60.35||
lekhām iva navām indoḥ prātaḥsūryaprabhām iva|
haviṣā hūyamānasya tanvīm agneḥ śikhām iva|| 60.36||
vijñāya sa tadā yogānmahāyogāṃ sureśvarīm|
īśvaro jagato viṣṇurjiṣṇustuṣṭāva pārvatīm|| 60.37||
tvaṃ sraṣṭrī sarvabhūtānāṃ saṃhartrī tvaṃ sureśvari|
tvam asya jagato dhātrī nityā prakṛtiravyayā|| 60.38||
tvaṃ prabhā śarvarī jyotsnā kīrtistuṣṭirumā dhṛtiḥ|
buddhirmedhā smṛtiḥ prajñā saṃdhyā kāntiḥ stutirmatiḥ|| 60.39||
tvam īśā devi devānāṃ gaṇamātā gaṇāmbikā|
bhadrakālī mahāgaurī kauśikī vindhyavāsinī|| 60.40||
durgā khyātirmahāvidyā gāyatrī tvaṃ sarasvatī|
svāhā svadhā mahāmāyā lakṣmī yogeśvareśvarī|| 60.41||
ulkā satī gireḥ putrī maineyī brahmacāriṇī|
tāpasī revatī ṣaṣṭhī varā varasahasradā|| 60.42||
kundakārmukasāraṅgakokilāśokapallavaiḥ|
tulyāsi dantabhrūnetrasvarapāṇibhirīśvari|| 60.43||
pramattotphullasaṃpūrṇān nāgotpalaniśākarān|
viśinakṣi sadā devi gatilocanakāntibhiḥ|| 60.44||
śirobhirmāhiṣairbhrāntaraktaparyantalocanaiḥ|
nṛbhiḥ kṣititalanyastakarajānubhirījyase|| 60.45||
mattānyapuṣṭākalavalgubhāṣitā dvirephamālāsitacārumūrdhajā|
praphullapuṣpastavakodgatastanī virājase kalpalateva puṣpitā|| 60.46||
devi devībhiraniśaṃ bhaktābhirvandyase divi|
ījyase munibhiḥ śaśvadgirije girimūrdhasu|| 60.47||
arcyase siddhagandharvairgandhapuṣpotkaraiḥ sadā|
sadāgatipathaprāptā prāptyā ca stūyase 'anaghe|| 60.48||
bhāsi siṃhaṃ samārūḍhā calatpiṅgalakesaram|
dīptā prabheva sāvitrī merormūrdhānam āsthitā|| 60.49||
jighāṃsatī raṇe daityāñcharaughairbhāsyajihmagaiḥ|
ravermūrtistamāṃsīva vikirantī gabhastibhiḥ|| 60.50||
paraśuṃ śitam udgṛhya devadānavasaṃyuge|
bhrājase devi saṃkruddhā pāṭayantīva rodasī|| 60.51||
atha sā śaiśavaṃ hitvā tanum anyāṃ samādade|
ekīkṛtām ivākāśe saṃhatiṃ sarvatejasām|| 60.52||
dīptām api sukhālokāṃ śāntām api savibhramām|
bālām api jagaddhātrīṃ tanvīm api susaṃhatām|| 60.53||
uvācedaṃ ca suprītā varadāsmi tava prabho|
evam uktastayā so 'atha provācāmbhodanisvanaḥ|| 60.54||
śaraṇye devi bhaktānāṃ śaraṇāgatavatsale|
bhavāni bhava me nityaṃ suprasannā maheśvari|| 60.55||
kathayasva ca deveśaṃ śāśvataṃ sthāṇum avyayam|
viśvātmānaṃ mahādevaṃ sarvayogeśvareśvaram|| 60.56||
tathāstviti pratijñāya kathayāmāsa śaṃkaram|
mṛgayūthasya madhyasthaṃ krīḍantaṃ mṛgarūpiṇam|| 60.57||
ekaśṛṅgaṃ mahāgrīvam ekākṣam amitaujasam|
ekapādaṃ susaṃśliṣṭam āpāṇḍukapilodaram|| 60.58||
atha viṣṇurdrutaṃ gatvā śṛṅge jagrāha taṃ prabhum|
tasminneva tato brahmā jagrāhendraśca vīryavān|| 60.59||
tridhā tadabhavacchṛṅgaṃ calite dīptatejasi|
trayāṇāṃ suramukhyānāṃ pṛthak pāṇiṣu saṃsthitam|| 60.60||
athādṛśyastadā śarvastānuvāca surottamān|
yadartham āgatā yūyaṃ tadbrūta surasattamāḥ|| 60.61||
athovāca tato brahmā parameśaṃ vṛṣadhvajam|
rājyaṃ punaravāpnotu hatvā vṛtraṃ puraṃdaraḥ|| 60.62||
tatastānamarāṃstatra vṛṣaketuḥ samāgatān|
svareṇa vāridadhvānagambhīreṇābravīt tadā|| 60.63||
vaiṣṇavaṃ paramaṃ tejaḥ phenam āvekṣyate surāḥ|
śiraśchetsyati vṛtrasya tadādāya śatakratuḥ|| 60.64||
hṛṣīkeśo 'atha tatkhaṇḍam anayat svaṃ niketanam|
nyaveśayata tatraiva vārijodarasaṃbhavaḥ|| 60.65||
nīyamānaṃ tṛtīyaṃ ca khaṇḍam ākhaṇḍalena tu|
rakṣasām adhipaḥ śrīmāñjagrāhātha daśānanaḥ|| 60.66||
cakāra saṃdhyām udadhau dakṣiṇe nyasya tat tadā|
na vicālayituṃ śaktaḥ saṃdhyām āsthāya rāvaṇaḥ|| 60.67||
tat puṇyaṃ devadevasya vyāsa kṣetraṃ mahādyuteḥ|
gokarṇam iti nāmāsya cakāra kamalāsanaḥ|| 60.68||
tatra gatvā naro bhaktyā praṇipatya maheśvaram|
aśvamedham avāpnoti sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 60.69||
gokarṇam uttaraṃ vyāsa sthāpitaṃ padmayoninā|
udanvataḥ sthitaṃ tīre svayam eva tu dakṣiṇe|| 60.70||
yaḥ śṛṇoti naro nityaṃ puṇyaṃ gokarṇasaṃbhavam|
sarvapāpavidhūtātmā sa yāti paramāṃ gatim|| 60.71||
atha tau dānavau vyāsa gokarṇam abhijagmatuḥ|
tatra ceraturatyugraṃ tapo 'ambupavanāśanau|| 60.72||
kasyacit tvatha kālasya viditvograṃ tayostapaḥ|
ājagāma tayoḥ pārśvaṃ brahmā suranamaskṛtaḥ|| 60.73||
atha tau viśvadhātāraṃ caturvaktraṃ pitāmaham|
apaśyatāṃ mahābāhū brahmāṇaṃ purataḥ sthitam|| 60.74||
śuklāmbaradharaṃ dīptaṃ śuklasraganulepanam|
ekīkṛtam asamprekṣyaṃ tejo dinakṛtām iva|| 60.75||
prīto 'asmi yuvayoḥ putrāvathovāca pitāmahaḥ|
anena tapasogreṇa varaṃ brūtam abhīpsitam|| 60.76||
amaratvaṃ tu vavrāte tau praṇamya pitāmaham|
brahmāhātha vinā devānamaratvaṃ na vidyate|| 60.77||
avaśyam eṣyo yuvayormṛtyurekena kenacit|
athāmaratvaṃ vavrāte parasparavadhaṃ vinā|| 60.78||
evam astviti tābhyāṃ taṃ varaṃ dattvā pitāmahaḥ|
haṃsayuktena yānena jagāma svaṃ niketanam|| 60.79||
asurāvapi tau tasmāt tapasogrādvirematuḥ|
ājagmaturniketaṃ svaṃ varaṃ labdhvā pitāmahāt|| 60.80||
varadānaṃ tato jñātvā daityāḥ pātālavāsinaḥ|
ājagmurdānavāścaiva tayoḥ pārśvaṃ mudānvitāḥ|| 60.81||
keśirmuro mayaḥ śambhuḥ kārtasvaramahāravau|
indraśatruḥ kalirdhundhurilvalo namucirdrumaḥ|| 60.82||
vātāpī dundubhirmeghaḥ prabhuranye ca dānavāḥ|
sarve kavacinaḥ śūrā gadāparighapāṇayaḥ|| 60.83||
ūcuśca śokamagnānām asmākaṃ śatrutāpanau|
yuvāṃ plavāvivāyātau śokasāgaratāraṇau|| 60.84||
pure pratibhaye ramye kāntāṃ nāma tataḥ sabhām|
ājagmustuṣṭamanaso dānavendrāḥ samāgatāḥ|| 60.85||
tasyāṃ prayaste vistīrṇe śātakaumbhe varāsane|
āsasāda mahābāhuḥ sundo dānavasattamaḥ|| 60.86||
nisundo 'anyat tato bheje hemaratnamayaṃ śubham|
āsasāda tato dhīmān kārtasvaramaye mayaḥ|| 60.87||
anye ca dānavā bhejurāsanāni tadā mune|
hemaratnavicitrāṇi bhāsvanti ca mahānti ca|| 60.88||
vireje sā sabhā tatra dānavendraiḥ samāgataiḥ|
sabalākaistaḍitvadbhiḥ pralaye dyaurivāmbudaiḥ|| 60.89||
athonnāmya śiro ratnamarīcipariveṣavat|
sundo vacanam āhettham ambhodarucirasvanaḥ|| 60.90||
dānavendrāḥ kariṣyāmi sarveṣām asrumārjanam|
vijitya devataiḥ sārdham indraṃ mahāhavamūrdhani|| 60.91||
prayāma daṃśitāḥ sarve sajjībhavata dānavāḥ|
trailokyavijayaṃ kartum udyatāyudhapāṇayaḥ|| 60.92||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā prabhuḥ prāhāsureśvaram|
yajñavratatapobhiśca niyamaiścāsuradviṣaḥ|| 60.93||
āpyāyayanti saṃrabdhāḥ śaśvadvarṇāśramā bhuvi|
tāneva prathamaṃ hatvā tato jeṣyāma devatāḥ|| 60.94||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā prāhurdānavasattamāḥ|
āyatiṃ prathamaṃ hatvā vijeṣyāmastato 'amarān|| 60.95||
tathā tebhyo vayam api procchritadhvajasaṃkule|
āneṣyāmo raṇe jitvā śriyam āvignalocanām|| 60.98||
apakāre sati same svabhāvena manasvinām|
tejo vijṛmbhate dīptaṃ śaktimatsveva sarvadā|| 60.99||
atha dhundhorvacaḥ śrutvā muro murajanisvanaḥ|
uccairutkṣipya mūrdhānaṃ provāca prahasanniva|| 60.100||
purābhūvan mahātmāno dānavendrā mahābalāḥ|
hiraṇyakaśipurvṛtraḥ prahlādo namucirbaliḥ|| 60.101||
koṭiśo dānavāścānye mahāsattvā mahābalāḥ|
yaiḥ kṛtā prasabhaṃ lakṣmī svavakṣaḥsthalavāsinī|| 60.102||
alpāvaśeṣairadhunā yuṣmābhirasurottamāḥ|
katham ānīyate rājyaṃ surān nirjitya saṃyuge|| 60.103||
iṣṭārthasādhakenāśu deśakālāvirodhinā|
upāyena parīpsadhvaṃ rājyam anyena kenacit|| 60.104||
etacchrutvā tadā vākyam aṃśumālī mahāsuraḥ|
provāca madhuraṃ ślakṣṇam arthānugam idaṃ vacaḥ|| 60.105||
sāparādhā balīyāṃso baddhavairāśca dānavaiḥ|
jayinaḥ śrīmadonmattāḥ sāma deveṣvanarthakam|| 60.106||
sureṣu mānasī siddhirvibhutā bhuvanatraye|
aṇimādyairguṇairyogasteṣu dānam apārthakam|| 60.107||
ekārthānarthinaḥ sarve saṃhatāścāsuradviṣaḥ|
na te bhedayituṃ śakyā dānavairdānavottamāḥ|| 60.108||
mantraprabhāvaśaktibhyām utsāhena pareṇa ca|
sampannāḥ sarvathā devā na yuddhaṃ taiḥ saheṣyate|| 60.109||
yukto dānavamukhyānāṃ hīnasaṃdhiḥ suraiḥ saha|
sthānavṛddhiparīpsūnāṃ kṣīṇānām adhunā bhṛśam|| 60.110||
athāha tejasā svena tejāṃsi suravidviṣām|
abhibhūya sadasyuccairaṃśumānaṃśumāniva|| 60.111||
praṇāmapūrvaḥ kriyate hīnasaṃdhiḥ kurājabhiḥ|
na cakrurdānavāḥ pūrvaṃ kurvate na ca sāmpratam|| 60.112||
śirāṃsi dānavendrāṇāṃ kathaṃ yāsyanti namratām|
sumeroriva śṛṅgāṇi bhānumantyucchritāni ca|| 60.113||
ādāsyāmo 'athavā rājyaṃ devān nirjitya saṃyuge|
prāpsyāmo vā gatiṃ puṇyāṃ nihatāḥ samare 'amaraiḥ|| 60.114||
ittham aṃśumataḥ śrutvā vākyaṃ vākyārthakovidaḥ|
gambhīram arthavat prāha mahiṣo vadatāṃ varaḥ|| 60.115||
viditaṃ vaḥ samastānāṃ pūrvajā bhavatāṃ yathā|
hatā dānavaśārdūlā vikramaikarasāḥ suraiḥ|| 60.116||
tadalaṃ dānavaśreṣṭhā vṛttyā vo 'agnipataṅgayoḥ|
saṃdhāya devataiḥ sārdhaṃ vṛttiṃ kurmaḥ svakarmabhiḥ|| 60.117||
jyāyobhirdānavā devai randhravyasanavarjitaiḥ|
vigraheṇa kathaṃ siddhim icchatha srastaśaktayaḥ|| 60.118||
guṇātiśayayuktānāṃ yānam abhyuccaye sati|
mantrotsāhaprabhāvānām avāptau deśakālayoḥ|| 60.119||
atha sambhūyayānena manyadhvaṃ siddhim ātmanaḥ|
daṃśitāḥ samare yattāḥ sametā yakṣarākṣasaiḥ|| 60.120||
rakṣāṃsi hutaśeṣāṇi jvalane śaktisūnunā|
śritāni devatāneva bhītānyabalavanti ca|| 60.121||
āyattāḥ sarvadā yakṣāḥ kubere 'asurasattamāḥ|
sa cāpi suramukhyānāṃ kurute kāryam udyataḥ|| 60.122||
anyatra daityaśatrubhyo bhuvaneṣu balīyasaḥ|
abhāvādasuraśreṣṭhā dvaidhībhāvo na vidyate|| 60.123||
mahiṣe sadasi svastham ityuktavati dānave|
vispaṣṭam arthavadvākyaṃ drumaḥ prāha mahāsuraḥ|| 60.124||
samare 'anirjitāḥ pūrvam asmābhirabalaiḥ saha|
jayinaḥ śaktisampannāḥ saṃdhāsyante kathaṃ surāḥ|| 60.125||
saṃvidhāyāśu durgāṇi pārvatānyaudakāni ca|
vijaye satataṃ yuktā vigṛhyāsanam āsmahe|| 60.126||
nāśayantaḥ sadā yajñān vratāni niyamāṃstathā|
varṇāśramāṃśca loke 'asmiñjighāṃsantaḥ samantataḥ|| 60.127||
tato lokavināśena vicchinne satkriyāpathe|
viditvāpacitān devānabhiyāsyāma daṃśitāḥ|| 60.128||
atha te tasya vacanaṃ sarva evānumenire|
āsannamṛtyavo 'apathyam annaṃ prāṇabhṛto yathā|| 60.129||
uttasthurlokanāśāya matiṃ kṛtvāmaradviṣaḥ|
udanvanta ivodvelāḥ pralaye mārutākulāḥ|| 60.130||
jalada iva sunīlaḥ pīnavṛttonnatāṅgo
tadanu tadanujo 'ambuvāhanīlaḥ parighabhujaḥ pṛthuraktadīrghanetraḥ|
ajahadavimanāḥ svam āsanāntaṃ pratibhayakṛddviṣatāṃ tadā nisundaḥ|| 60.132||
iti skandapurāṇe ṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 60.60||

ekaṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha dānavamukhyānāṃ lokanāśāya niryayau|
mattavāraṇasambādhaṃ rathāśvakalilaṃ balam|| 61.1||
tat tadā dānavānīkaṃ visasāra diśo diśaḥ|
pralaye mārutoddhūtam udanvata ivodakam|| 61.2||
nijaghnurbrāhmaṇān kecit kecinniṣpipiṣurviśaḥ|
susubhuḥ kṣatriyānanye śūdrānanye babhakṣire|| 61.3||
jagrasurlilihurnedurbabhañjuśca samantataḥ|
yajñeṣvannaṃ havirnādān yūpāṃścāmaravidviṣaḥ|| 61.4||
svadhītavedādhyayanābhināditān munipravekācitagulmapādapān|
prabhūtacīrājinadarbhasaṃcayān nikāmaparyantahimāmbunirjharān|| 61.5||
upāntanīvāragavedhukācitān prasuptaviśvastamṛgarkṣavānarān|
havirbhujo dhūmavitānasaṃkulān visṛtya cānye parijaghnurāśramān|| 61.6||
kecinmunīnām asurā jīrṇoragasamatviṣaḥ|
jaṭāḥ saṃgṛhya lulucuḥ kṣālitāstīrthavāriṇā|| 61.7||
pātayitvāsurāḥ keciccaraṇaiḥ pipiṣuḥ kṣitau|
ṛṣīn ātmavināśāya hutāśāñjvalitāniva|| 61.8||
śirāṃsi munipatnīnāṃ karaiḥ kecit talatribhiḥ|
pūtāni vāribhiḥ puṇyaiḥ paspṛśurdānavādhamāḥ|| 61.9||
atha te jagṛhuryātrāṃ jñātvābhyudayam ātmanaḥ|
vikṣiptaṃ lokanāśāya balam āhūya sarvaśaḥ|| 61.10||
praśaste 'ahani nakṣatre muhūrte ca jayānvite|
saṃnāhabherīrāhatya kriyāścakrurjayāvahāḥ|| 61.11||
saṃnāhyān balino mattān ānāyya varavāraṇān|
samyagabhyarcya varmāṇi babandhurvidhināsurāḥ|| 61.12||
yantrāṇi dhautairnārācaiḥ pūrṇāni āsanapārśvayoḥ|
babandhuḥ śaktipūrṇāṃśca veṇūṃstiryagavasthitān|| 61.13||
tomarān kaṇapāñchaṃkūñchūlacakraparaśvadhān|
ābabandhurniyuktāṃśca madhyamāsanapārśvayoḥ|| 61.14||
sajjāni paramāstrāṇi bāṇadhīṃśca susaṃskṛtān|
sampūrṇān gārdhravāsobhirniśitāgraiḥ śilīmukhaiḥ|| 61.15||
saṃnāhyānaṅkuśā/llohān bālendusadṛśadyutīn|
graiveyeṣu sitāṃścakrurmadhye mastakapiṇḍayoḥ|| 61.16||
kṣurapramālāḥ saṃyastāḥ śātakumbhamayīḥ śubhāḥ|
ābabandhuśca kumbheṣu gajānāṃ gajasādinaḥ|| 61.17||
vaijayantīpatākāśca vicitrāḥ svabhilakṣitāḥ|
ucchrayāmāsurāyattā dantyanīkasya dānavāḥ|| 61.18||
ghaṇṭā vāraṇamukhyānām āsasañjurmahāsvanāḥ|
cāmarāṇi sudīrghāṇi haṃsāṃsarucirāṇi ca|| 61.19||
ekaikasya catasraśca kareṇvaścārudarśanāḥ|
sthāpitāḥ purato daityaiḥ paravāraṇavāraṇāḥ|| 61.20||
yūno yuvabhirārūḍhāñchikṣitānastrakovidaiḥ|
cakruragresarānaśvān varmiṇo lohajālinaḥ|| 61.21||
varmiṇo baddhakavacāñchitanistriṃśadhāriṇaḥ|
teṣāṃ puraḥsarān pattīnanuyātāṃśca dhanvibhiḥ|| 61.22||
daityayodhāstataścānye varmiṇo lohajālinaḥ|
ārūḍhā baddhanistriṃśāḥ snātapītāṃsturaṃgamān|| 61.23||
kecidvinītairyuvabhiḥ snāpitaiḥ kṛtamaṅgalaiḥ|
rathān saṃyojayāmāsuraśvairagrajavaistadā|| 61.24||
sāyudhān sapatākāṃśca kiṃkiṇījālanāditān|
adhitasthustadā kecidrathān hāṭakasaṃskṛtān|| 61.25||
evaṃ tat kalpitaṃ śrutvā sainyaṃ sainyanamaskṛtaḥ|
sundo dānavaśārdūlo niryayau kṛtamaṅgalaḥ|| 61.26||
svīṣaṃ sukūbaraṃ svakṣaṃ śātakumbhamayaṃ varam|
nānāmaṇimayaiścitrairbhaktipuṣpamṛgadvijaiḥ|| 61.27||
yuktaṃ paramasaṃhṛṣṭairmanovegaisturaṃgamaiḥ|
āruhyātha rathaṃ divyaṃ patākādhvajaśobhitam|| 61.28||
kavacī baddhanistriṃśo vidhūtasitacāmaraḥ|
abhitaḥ stūyamānaśca sūtamāgadhavandibhiḥ|| 61.29||
nisundo 'api madaśyāmakapolālīnaṣaṭpadam|
āruhya nirjagāmāśu saṃgrāmikam anekapam|| 61.30||
anye ca dānavāstatra rathairaśvairmataṅgajaiḥ|
niryayuḥ paramaprītyā yuddhaśauṇḍāḥ sudaṃśitāḥ|| 61.31||
balasyāgresaraṃ kṛtvā tārakākṣaṃ mahāsuram|
sahitaṃ bahubhiḥ śūrai rathanāgāśvapattibhiḥ|| 61.32||
pṛṣṭhataḥ saṃvidhāyāśu balonmattaṃ mahāsuram|
balena caturaṅgena mahiṣaṃ parirakṣaṇam|| 61.33||
pārśvayorubhayornyasya meghasvanamahāsvanau|
sainyena mahatā guptau dānavāvarisūdanau|| 61.34||
madhye sundo nisundaśca mayaḥ śambhuḥ kharo muraḥ|
saṃnaddhā balinaḥ śūrāḥ parasainyanivāraṇāḥ|| 61.35||
pratasthire susaṃyattā divaṃ dānavasattamāḥ|
pralaye mārutoddhūtā ghanāḥ saṃvartakā iva|| 61.36||
teṣām āgamanaṃ jñātvā saha svarlokavāsibhiḥ|
apasṛtya jagāmāśu janasthānaṃ śatakratuḥ|| 61.37||
meroḥ śikharam āruhya sarve 'atha sahitāstadā|
senāṃ niveśayāmāsurnandane te suradviṣaḥ|| 61.38||
atha sainyasya daityendrā rakṣām ādhāya sarvaśaḥ|
pravibhaktānasambādhān āvāsāñjagṛhustataḥ|| 61.39||
dattānujñāstataḥ sarve dānavā dānavottamaiḥ|
saṃnāhyam apaninyuste sarvopakaraṇaṃ tadā|| 61.40||
ārūḍhā gajakanyāsu varmāṇi mumucuḥ śanaiḥ|
āyudhānyapanīyāśu sainikā mattadantinām|| 61.41||
saṃnāhānapaninyuśca mumucuḥ kavacāni ca|
tanutrāṇi vicitrāṇi tadā dānavasainikāḥ|| 61.42||
apetakakṣān mātaṅgān snātapītān gataklamān|
babandhuḥ kalpavṛkṣeṣu keciddānavasainikāḥ|| 61.43||
kecit kalpadrumān nāgā madasaṃlīnaṣaṭpadāḥ|
babhañjurbalinastrastamattodbhrāntavihaṅgamān|| 61.44||
jagharṣurbalinaḥ kecinmadaśyāmān mataṅgajāḥ|
kapolān kalpavṛkṣeṣu puṣpālīnālipaṃktiṣu|| 61.45||
nāgā jagāhire kecinmattā mandākinīṃ nadīm|
haimavārijakiñjalkapiñjaropāntarodhasam|| 61.46||
vimuktasāṃgrāmikavarmajālān prasannacittān parighṛṣṭakāyān|
nipītatoyānapanītakhedān babandhuraśvān pṛthagaśvabandhāḥ|| 61.47||
atha sūkṣmāṇi vāsāṃsi vicitrāḥ paramasrajaḥ|
āninyuḥ kalpavṛkṣebhyaḥ phalāni madhu cāsurāḥ|| 61.48||
haimāni kecit padmāni tadrajoruṇamūrtayaḥ|
babhañjurdānavā hṛṣṭā gatā mandākinīṃ nadīm|| 61.49||
āninyuḥ sainikāḥ kecinmandārakusumotkarān|
phalāni ājahrire kecit svādūni ca bahūni ca|| 61.50||
tatroṣya rajanīm ekāṃ bherīrāhatya dānavāḥ|
tenaiva vidhinā yattāḥ prajagmuramarāvatīm|| 61.51||
tatastūryaninādena gajānāṃ bṛṃhitena ca|
siṃhanādaiśca daityānāṃ cacālevāmarāvatī|| 61.52||
atha śūnyāṃ samudvīkṣya purīṃ dānavasattamāḥ|
ittham ūcuḥ susaṃhṛṣṭā nadanto bhairavasvanam|| 61.53||
jayati vibudhaśatruḥ sundadaityendrasiṃhaḥ
tadanu jayati cāruprāntaraktāyatākṣo
iti skandapurāṇa ekaṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 61.61||

dviṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha nirjitya daityendrau divaṃ vikramaśālinau|
jagmatuḥ sahitau daityairvindhyaṃ tuṅgaśiloccayam|| 62.1||
sampūjya vidhivaddaityān prasthāpya bhrātarau tadā|
remāte vindhyapādeṣu phullapādapasānuṣu|| 62.2||
daityābhyām atha vijñāya brahmā suraparābhavam|
vicintyaikamanāḥ samyagvadhopāyaṃ tayostadā|| 62.3||
tilaṃ tilaṃ samādāya ratnebhyaścārudarśanām|
sasarja kāmanīyāṅgīm aṅganāṃ valgunisvanām|| 62.4||
tilottameti tasyāśca nāma cakre pitāmahaḥ|
divyānām api sā strīṇām upameva tadā babhau|| 62.5||
atisampūrṇavaktrāṃ tām atīndīvaralocanām|
atihaṃsasvanālāpām atimattebhagāminīm|| 62.6||
lakṣmīrnirīkṣya savrīḍā paṅkajenāvṛṇonmukham|
vapurbhiścaiva cārvaṅgyāstrepurudyānadevatāḥ|| 62.7||
tām utpādya tato dhātā pākaśāsanam abravīt|
śambhunā madanaḥ pūrvaṃ nirdagdho locanāgninā|| 62.8||
tasya prodbhūtaye yāma sarve pārśvaṃ pinākinaḥ|
tam ārādhya tataḥ kurmo yathā syānmadanaḥ punaḥ|| 62.9||
atha te brahmaṇā sārdhaṃ tayā cāsuravidviṣaḥ|
jagmurvindhyagireḥ śṛṅgaṃ yatrāste bhagavān haraḥ|| 62.10||
tatra śarvam apaśyanto dagdhuste surasattamāḥ|
gṛṇantaḥ praṇavaṃ sarve śivasanyastacetasaḥ|| 62.11||
atha liṅgaṃ samuttasthau teṣāṃ madhye divaukasām|
susaṃhataṃ susaṃśliṣṭaṃ samūhastejasām iva|| 62.12||
uccacāra tadā tasmāduccairvāgviśadākṣarā|
nirdagdho 'ayaṃ mayā pāpastapasvijanakaṇṭakaḥ|| 62.13||
yuṣmadarthe vimokṣyāmi kāryaṃ vo 'ayaṃ kariṣyati|
karotu paritaśceyaṃ māṃ pradakṣiṇam aṅganā|| 62.14||
evam uktā maheśena sā cakāra pradakṣiṇām|
sannidhāyāñjaliṃ mūrdhni raktendīvarakomalam|| 62.15||
neme mūrtiṃ tadā pūrvāṃ nissasāra tato mukham|
tryakṣaṃ prasannabimboṣṭham amitadyuti kāntimat|| 62.16||
atha tejo viniḥsṛtya vadanendoḥ pinākinaḥ|
tāṃ viveśāṅganām āśu śaradbhāskarabhāsvaram|| 62.17||
atha sā dakṣiṇāṃ mūrtiṃ praṇeme cārudarśanā|
nirjagāma tadā dīptaṃ mukhaṃ suragurostataḥ|| 62.18||
vāribhārālasāmbhodarucimadbhīmanisvanam|
karāladaśanodbhāsi dīptaraktāntalocanam|| 62.19||
atyādityaṃ tatastejo mukhānniḥsṛtya dakṣiṇāt|
dṛśyamānaṃ suraiḥ sarvairviveśa pramadottamām|| 62.20||
praṇeme sā tatastasya paścimāṃ mūrtim añjasā|
niścakrāma tatastasyā mukhaṃ tryakṣam anuttamam|| 62.21||
tatastejo viniḥsṛtya mukhendormadanadviṣaḥ|
dīpyamānaṃ viveśāśu tām eva pramadottamām|| 62.22||
uttarāṃ mūrtim āgatya praṇeme sā kṛtāñjaliḥ|
tasyā mukhaṃ susampūrṇaṃ suprasannaṃ viniryayau|| 62.23||
tasmāt tejo viniḥsṛtya sūryadīptānalaprabham|
viveśa pramadām āśu tām eva varavarṇinīm|| 62.24||
mukhāni devadevasya surāṇām arthasiddhaye|
catvāri niryayurdikṣu na tasyā rūpavismayāt|| 62.25||
ātmasaṃsthaṃ purā tejo dagdhvā yanmadanaṃ kṛtam|
anujagrāha deveśastena tāṃ pramadottamām|| 62.26||
abravīcca surān sarvāṃstatredaṃ vacanaṃ śivaḥ|
yasmādiyaṃ māṃ yuṣmāṃśca maṇḍalena pradakṣiṇam|| 62.27||
cakre sarvān suraśreṣṭhāḥ sthānaṃ tasmādidaṃ mama|
bhaviṣyati girau vindhye maṇḍaleśvarasaṃjñitam|| 62.28||
maṇḍaleśvaram etacca yaḥ karoti pradakṣiṇam|
pradakṣiṇīkṛtā tena saptadvīpā mahī bhavet|
sānnidhyaṃ sarvadā hyasmin kariṣyāmi varapradaḥ|| 62.29||
maṇḍaleśvaram īśānaṃ dṛṣṭvā tu prayato naraḥ|
aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya mama lokam avāpsyati|| 62.30||
naikasiddhasamākīrṇaṃ kinnaroragasevitaṃ |
yuṣmābhiḥ sarvadā yuktaṃ bhaviṣyati mama priyam|| 62.31||
eṣā tilottamā caiva yadarthaṃ surasattamāḥ|
sṛṣṭā yuṣmābhiravyagrā tadvaḥ kāryaṃ kariṣyati|| 62.32||
etām avekṣya tau daityau mohitau madanārditau|
anyonyaṃ yāsyato nāśam eṣā caiva bhaviṣyati|| 62.33||
ajarā cāmarā caiva sarvāpsaravarā śubhā|
pūjyā ceha sadā sthāne vandyā caiva bhaviṣyati|| 62.34||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam ukte maheśena surāḥ suprītacetasaḥ|
tāṃ striyaṃ preṣayāmāsurvadhārthaṃ daityayostadā|| 62.35||
sahāyān pradadau cāsyai brahmā kamalavāhanaḥ|
krodhaṃ darpam ṛtūn sarvān mātsaryaṃ madam eva ca|| 62.36||
kālaṃ mṛtyuṃ ca mohaṃ ca viṣādaṃ cāmitadyutiḥ|
atha sampreṣayitvā tu devatāstāṃ tilottamām|| 62.37||
ātmānaṃ piṇḍayāmāsurdevāste sarva eva hi|
kaḥ kaḥ katama āyāta ihādyeti surarṣabhāḥ|| 62.38||
tato madhye sthitaṃ natvā bhūyaste parameśvaram|
piṇḍyamāneṣu deveṣu yasmānmadhye samasthitaḥ|| 62.39||
piṇḍāreśvara ityeva tatrāsāvabhavat tataḥ|
piṇḍāreśvaram īśānaṃ dṛṣṭvā bhaktyā tu mānavaḥ|| 62.40||
sarvāśubhavinirmukto dehabhede gaṇo bhavet|
pṛthivyāṃ yāni liṅgāni caturmukhāyatāni ca|| 62.41||
tāni sarvāṇi dṛśyāṇi idaṃ dṛṣṭvā bhavanti hi|
tatastā devatāḥ sarvāḥ kṛtvā kāryam atandritāḥ|| 62.42||
praṇamya parameśānaṃ svāni sadmāni bhejire|
sāpi cārumukhāpāṅgī pīnonnatapayodharā|| 62.43||
ākṣipantīva cetāṃsi surāṇāṃ vibhramaistadā|
pratasthe dakṣiṇām āśām āsāte yatra dānavau|| 62.44||
vindhyapādeṣu ramyeṣu vihagodgītasānuṣu|
bhramantāvatha daityendrau sthitāṃ dadṛśatustu tām|| 62.45||
aśokaśākhām utphullām ālambyonmattaṣaṭpadām|
vasānām aṃśukaṃ citram ābaddhamaṇimekhalām|| 62.46||
gāyantīṃ madhuraṃ raktaṃ samaṃ kalam anākulam|
tāramandrātitāraiśca svaraiḥ samyagalaṃkṛtam|| 62.47||
sākṣādiva tapaḥsiddhiṃ śritaṃ mūrtimatīm iva|
prāptām iva ratiṃ sākṣāt kāntiṃ cāndramasīm iva|| 62.48||
mamaiveyaṃ mamaiveyam iti tau dānavottamau|
abhisṛtya tu tau devīṃ pāṇyorjagṛhatuḥ samam|| 62.49||
atha darpamadakrodhamātsaryāviṣṭacetasau|
tau cukrudhaturatyartham anyonyasyāsurottamau|| 62.50||
tayorgade 'antakaḥ kālo mṛtyuścāviviśurdrutam|
pragṛhyātha gade kruddhāvanyonyam abhijaghnatuḥ|| 62.51||
athaikaikena tau tatra prahāreṇābhitāḍitau|
viṣaṇṇau bhinnasarvāṅgau śivaśāpavimohitau|| 62.52||
visaṃjñau patitau bhūmau cchinnamūlāviva drumau|
atha niryayatustatra kāmopahatacetasau|| 62.53||
ātmānau saha śukreṇa tayordānavamukhyayoḥ|
tau tadā nirgatau tatra tayorjīvau durātmanoḥ|| 62.54||
balinau cārusarvāṅgau bālau āśu babhūvatuḥ|
ekastatrābravīdbālaḥ śumbho 'ahaṃ dviṣatām iti|| 62.55||
niśumbho 'apyaham anyastu bālastatrāvadat tadā|
atha vindhyaḥ samāsādya bālau tāvamitadyutī|| 62.56||
ādideśātmanaḥ patnīṃ pāhi tvaṃ bālakāviti|
vavṛdhāte 'atha tau tatra dānavendrasutāvubhau|| 62.57||
kṛṣṇapakṣakṣaye yadvadyugapacchaśisāgarau|
buddhvā tau ca tadā janma dānavābhyām arindamau|| 62.58||
tapaśceraturatyugraṃ parṇāmbupavanāśanau|
tapasārādhitastābhyāṃ tatrāgatyābravīt prabhuḥ|| 62.59||
tuṣṭo 'asmi yuvayoḥ putrau varaṃ kiṃ vā dadānyaham|
vavrāte tau varaṃ vīrāvajayyāvadhyatāṃ sadā|| 62.60||
prārthanāṃ tāṃ tayoḥ śrutvā pratyuvāca pitāmahaḥ|
avaśyaṃ yuvayoreṣyaṃ maraṇaṃ yena kenacit|| 62.61||
surebhyo 'anyatra daityendrāvamaratvaṃ na vidyate|
ityuktavantaṃ brahmāṇaṃ vavrāte dānavau varam|| 62.62||
ubhāvapi suniścitya samprahṛṣṭatanūruhau|
jaganmātuśca yā kanyā vinā tasyāḥ pitāmaha|| 62.63||
mā bhūtām āvayordeva sadā mṛtyuparājayau|
evam astviti tau procya daityendratanayāvubhau|| 62.64||
viśvasya jagataḥ sraṣṭā tatraivāntaradhīyata|
atha tau tapasastīvrādviramya kṛtamaṅgalau|| 62.65||
maulinau baddhakavacau hārāṅgadavibhūṣitau|
haricandanadigdhāṅgau pītakauśeyavāsasau|| 62.66||
vindhyaprastheṣu ramyeṣu ceraturdānavottamau|
pitāmahādvaraprāptiṃ śrutvā śumbhaniśumbhayoḥ|| 62.67||
ājagmurdānavā hṛṣṭāḥ pātālatalavāsinaḥ|
śambhurmayo ghanaḥ keśirnarako namucirdrumaḥ|| 62.68||
anye ca koṭiśo dṛptā hataśeṣāḥ suradviṣaḥ|
vindhyaprasthe niṣeduste sametāḥ sarvadānavāḥ|| 62.69||
nānādrumalatāgulmavikīrṇakusumotkare|
dhanvino baddhanistriṃśāścitrābharaṇabhūṣitāḥ|| 62.70||
sendracāpāstaḍitvanto nabhasīva balāhakāḥ|
athovāca mayastatra dānavo dānavottamau|| 62.71||
pitṛbhyāṃ yuvayorbhuktaṃ trailokyam akhilaṃ purā|
yuvābhyām adhunā daityau kasmānnādīyate punaḥ|| 62.72||
sametānamarān sarvān nirjitya raṇamūrdhani|
ye sahāyā hi vāṃ pitrorbabhūvuḥ suravidviṣaḥ|| 62.73||
ta evāmī balonmattāḥ sahāyā yuvayoryudhi|
ityuktavati daityendre maye śumbho mahāsuraḥ|| 62.74||
niśumbhasya mukhaṃ prekṣya vākyam itthaṃ tadābravīt |
bhūrlokam akhilaṃ daityā yuṣmābhiḥ saha sāmpratam|| 62.75||
saṃvibhajya surān sarvāñjeṣyāmo raṇamūrdhani|
jambūdvīpaṃ svayaṃ so 'atha jagrāhāsurasattamaḥ|| 62.76||
śākadvīpaṃ niśumbhāya dadau bhrātre kanīyase|
śālmalidvīpagomedau dānavebhyo dadau prabhuḥ|| 62.77||
krauṅcadvīpakuśadvīpau daityebhyaḥ pradadau ca saḥ|
daityendraḥ puṣkaradvīpaṃ bhārgavāya nyavedayat|| 62.78||
evaṃ prativibhajyāśu bhūrlokam akhilaṃ tadā|
ijyāñjalinamaskārān yajñān sarvāśca satkriyāḥ|| 62.79||
ācchidya daivatebhyaste jagṛhurdaityadānavāḥ|
babhūvātha tato yajñaḥ kaśyapasya mahātmanaḥ|| 62.80||
āgatya taṃ tadā yajñaṃ mamṛduḥ suraśatravaḥ|
ādhipatyaṃ hi naḥ kṛtsne bhūrloke kaśyapādhunā|| 62.81||
sarvāvasthāsu yajñe 'asminnasmāṃstvaṃ yaṣṭum arhasi|
evam uktastato daityairmārīcaḥ kaśyapastadā|| 62.82||
gambhīram arthavadvākyam uvācetthaṃ smayanniva|
trailokyam ātmanaḥ kṛtvā jitvā sarvāmarān raṇe|| 62.83||
yajñabhāgāṃstato daityāḥ sarvān ādātum arhatha|
evam uktāstadā tena daityadānavasattamāḥ|| 62.84||
balaṃ sarvaṃ samādāya kṛtvā sāṅgramikīḥ kriyāḥ|
praśasteṣu kṛtācārā muhūrtarkṣadineṣu te|| 62.85||
rathairnāgaisturaṅgaiśca niryayurdaityadānavāḥ|
pṛṣṭhataḥ purataḥ samyak pārśvayorubhayorapi|| 62.86||
vidhāya rakṣāṃ saṃyattā yayurdevāñjigīṣavaḥ|
teṣām āgamanaṃ jñātvā dviṣatāṃ pākaśāsanaḥ|| 62.87||
saṃhatānāṃ susaṃyatto yuddhvā nākaṃ jigīṣatām|
vidhiṃ vidhāya svapure samastaṃ daurgakarmikam|| 62.88||
puṇyeṣu tithinakṣatramuhūrtakaraṇeṣu saḥ|
munīn vidhivadabhyarcya namaskṛtvā pinākine|| 62.89||
sārdhaṃ suragaṇaiḥ sarvairniryayau kṛtamaṅgalaḥ|
himavacchikharākāraṃ caturdantam anekapam|| 62.90||
āruhyairāvataṃ śaśvanmadatoyaughavarṣiṇam|
mahatā haimadaṇḍena ratnāṃśupariveṣiṇā|| 62.91||
ucchriteṇātapatreṇa dhriyamāṇena bhāsvatā|
vījyamānaḥ śaraccandrakiraṇotkaranirmalaiḥ|| 62.92||
cāmarai ratnadaṇḍāṃśusamūhakhacitodaraiḥ|
āśīrbhirjayaśabdaiśca munibhiḥ parivarddhitaḥ|| 62.93||
abhitaḥ stūyamānaśca sūtamāgadhavandibhiḥ|
athāvakāśe vistīrṇe same pādapavarjite|| 62.94||
racayāmāsa devānāṃ padmavyūhaṃ bṛhaspatiḥ|
marudbhiḥ sahitaṃ kṛtvā karṇikāyāṃ śatakratum|| 62.95||
patreṣu ca vasūn rudrān ādityāṃśca nyaveśayat|
keśareṣu yamaṃ kālaṃ kuberavaruṇāvapi|| 62.96||
anantaṃ sahitaṃ nāgairnāle gururakalpayat|
devānanyān sametāṃśca rakṣogandharvasenayā|| 62.97||
punaḥ saraḥ sa padmasya paritaḥ paryakalpayat|
atha dānavatūryāṇāṃ śabdaṃ śrutvā divaukasaḥ|| 62.98||
ājaghnurmuditā bherīrnedurnādāṃśca saṃghaśaḥ|
vimiśrāṃstūryaśabdena śrutvā nādān divaukasām|| 62.99||
saṃyattāḥ sutarāṃ cakruḥ prayatnaṃ dānaveśvarāḥ|
atha te dānavā dṛṣṭvā padmavyūhaṃ divaukasām|| 62.100||
papracchurbhārgavaṃ tatra tadbhedam amitaujasaḥ|
sa pṛṣṭo dānavaśreṣṭhairvyūhabhedam anākulaḥ|| 62.101||
vicintya bhārgavo dhīmān ītham āhāsurāṃstadā|
vikīrṇāḥ paritaḥ sarve tuṣāranikarā iva|| 62.102||
padmavyūhaṃ surendrāṇāṃ hata samyak suradviṣaḥ|
evam uktāstato daityā bhārgaveṇa mahātmanā|| 62.103||
siṃhanādaṃ vinadyāśu paritaste 'abhisaṃpatan|
tato yuddhaṃ samabhavaddevadānavasainyayoḥ|| 62.104||
āyudhairvividhaistīkṣṇaiḥ parasparam abhighnatoḥ|
sādinaḥ sādibhiḥ sārdhaṃ nāgā nāgai rathā rathaiḥ|| 62.105||
pattayaḥ pattibhirdṛptairdṛptā yuyudhire yudhi|
kecidvibhinnā nārācaiśchinnāḥ kecit paraśvadhaiḥ|| 62.106||
nipeturvasavo yodhāḥ senayorubhayorapi|
chindhi bhindhi sahedānīṃ tiṣṭha mūḍha kva gacchasi|| 62.107||
iti vācaḥ sumuttasthuryudhi yodhairudīritāḥ|
vasārudhirasaṃsiktaṃ tanutrāvaraṇācitam|| 62.108||
hatanāgāśvakalalaṃ tadbabhūva raṇājiram|
atha tairdānavaistatra pīḍyamānā divaukasaḥ|| 62.109||
savraṇā hatabhūyiṣṭhāḥ śakram evābhiśiśriyuḥ|
anantaṃ nāgamukhyāśca kuberaṃ yakṣarākṣasāḥ|| 62.110||
bhinne vyūhe 'atha devānāṃ prahṛṣṭā daityadānavāḥ|
siṃhanādān vinadyoccaistūryāṇi āhatya bhūyaśaḥ|| 62.111||
abhyadravantaḥ saṃyattāḥ samare pākaśāsanam|
athotthāpya gajaṃ śakro vajreṇa śataparvaṇā|| 62.112||
cūrṇayāmāsa saṃkruddho daityadānavavāhinīm|
dadāha dānavānīkaṃ paritaḥ pākaśāsanaḥ|| 62.113||
nidāghasamaye dīptaḥ śuṣkakakṣam ivānalaḥ|
atha śumbhaḥ samabhyetya samare śakram abravīt || 62.114||
dṛṣṭo 'asyadya mayā śakra na jīvan pratiyāsyasi|
athāgatya tadā brahmā prāhetthaṃ surasattamān|| 62.115||
na yoddhavyaṃ surā daityairavadhyā vaḥ suradviṣaḥ|
na yoddhavyaṃ na yoddhavyaṃ surā daityairmahābalaiḥ|| 62.116||
pūrvalabdhavarā hyete avadhyāśca suradviṣaḥ|
antardadhustatastasya vākyaṃ śrutvā divaukasaḥ|
vihāya samaraṃ sarve kṣipraṃ sabalavāhanāḥ|| 62.117||
atha daityāḥ susaṃhṛṣṭāstūryāṇi āhatya bhūyaśaḥ|
neduruccairvacaścedam ūcuḥ samaraśālinaḥ|| 62.118||
turagakhurapuṭāntakṣuṇṇareṇvandhakāre dviradarathaninādatrastapādātavṛnde|
vigatabhayaviṣādaḥ saṃyuge śuṃbhasiṃho jayati suravijetā vārivāhorunādaḥ|| 62.119||
tadanu jayati dīrghapīnathubāhuḥ pṛthurucironnatasaṃhatoruvakṣāḥ|
mṛgapatigamano 'ambuvāhanādaḥ samaravare vijayī niśuṃbhasiṃhaḥ|| 62.120||
iti skandapurāṇe devāsurasaṃgrāme
śuṃbhaniśuṃbhavijayso nāma
dviṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 62.62||

triṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
atha nirjitya samare devān devadviṣastadā|
ājagmuḥ sahitā vindhyaṃ śikharālīnatoyadam|| 63.1||
prasthāpya vidhivat sarvāṃstau tadā daityadānavān|
remāte sahitau vindhye kinnarodgītakandare|| 63.2||
ārakṣitastayostatra mūko nāma mahāsuraḥ|
apaśyacchikhare devīṃ jvalantīm iva tejasā|| 63.3||
puṇyalakṣaṇasaṃpūrṇāṃ puṇyābharaṇabhūṣitām|
āgatāṃ tatra tāṃ siddhiṃ puṇyānāṃ karmaṇām iva|| 63.4||
atha mūkastadā devīṃ vismayotphullalocanaḥ|
dṛṣṭvā jagāma manasā śuṃbhaṃ dānavasattmam|| 63.5||
yatheyaṃ cārusarvāṅgī pradhānā sarvayoṣitām|
tathā puṃsāṃ pradhāno 'asau śumbho daityendracandramāḥ|| 63.6||
vistīrṇavakṣasastasya viśālajaghanasthalā|
anurūpā bhavet patnī dīrghākṣasyāsitekṣaṇā|| 63.7||
iti saṃcintya manasā tām uvāca sumadhyamām|
kā tvaṃ trastasamudbhrāntamṛgaśāvavilocane|| 63.8||
kaḥ pitā te 'anavadyāṅgi kā vā mātā tavānaghe|
kimarthaṃ vā vasasyatra girau dānavasevite|| 63.9||
evam uktātha mūkena mahāyogā sureśvarī|
vijñāya manasā kālaṃ prāptaṃ śumbhaniśumbhayoḥ|| 63.10||
smitapūrvam idaṃ prāha vākyaṃ vākyaviśāradā|
mānuṣīṃ māṃ vijānīhi girāvasmin kṛtālayām|| 63.11||
ātreyaḥ svargato vidvān pitā cakracaro mama|
vihāya māṃ puro bālāṃ mātāpyanugatā patim|| 63.12||
ājñaptāsmi tadā mātrā pradāyāstrāṇi dānava|
vasa vindhye girau ramye yogaṃ ca kuru sarvadā|| 63.13||
sāhaṃ vacanam āryāyāḥ pālayantī nagottame|
vasāmi siṃhaśārdūlamātaṅgamṛgasevite|| 63.14||
iti devyā vacaḥ śrutvā mūkaḥ saṃhṛṣṭamānasaḥ|
jagāma dānavaśreṣṭhaṃ śumbhaṃ draṣṭuṃ kṛtatvaraḥ|| 63.15||
atha śuṃbhaṃ samāsādya harṣeṇotphullalocanaḥ|
ācacakṣa ivākārairapūrvaṃ ratnadarśanam|| 63.16||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā vismayotphullaṃ raktāyatavilocanaḥ|
mūkam āha tadā śumbhaḥ kasmāt tuṣṭo 'asi dānava|| 63.17||
evam uktaḥ sa śuṃbhena mūko vacanam abravīt|
apūrvam adya dṛṣṭaṃ me strīratnaṃ śikhare gireḥ|| 63.18||
na tādṛśī manuṣyeṣu na deveṣvapi sundarī|
na rakṣassu na yakṣeṣu na gandharvapureṣu vā|| 63.19||
na nāgeṣu na siddheṣu na daityapativeśmasu|
dṛṣṭapūrvā mayā rājan yādṛśī sā varāṅganā|| 63.20||
kā tvaṃ kasya kimarthaṃ vā vasasīha girāviti|
pṛṣṭābravīnmayā vākyam ātreyaduhitā hyaham|| 63.21||
vasāmi cātra vindhyasya śikhare māturājñayā|
iti bhartuḥ samākhyāya virarāma sa dānavaḥ|| 63.22||
atha śuṃbhasya hṛdaye mūkasya vacasā saha|
kāmo 'avakāśam akarodvināśāya suradviṣām|| 63.23||
tataḥ provāca daityendraḥ kāmākulitamānasaḥ|
gaccha mūka madarthe tāṃ pralobhaya sumadhyamā|| 63.24||
evam uktaḥ sa śuṃbhena drutam utthāya dānavaḥ|
prayayau yatra sā devī prāganenābhilakṣitā|| 63.25||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā dānavaṃ devī kṛtāñjalim upasthitam|
kimartham āgato 'asīti mūkaṃ pṛṣṭavatī tadā|| 63.26||
evaṃ pṛṣṭo 'atha kauśikyā prāhetthaṃ mūkadānavaḥ|
ārye dūto 'asmi śumbhasya tvatsamīpam upāgataḥ|| 63.27||
atha devī smitaṃ kṛtvā prasannam abhivīkṣya tam|
ittham āhāgataṃ dūtaṃ kiṃ sa āhāsureśvaraḥ|| 63.28||
iti pṛṣṭastadā devyā prāha mūkaḥ kṛtāñjaliḥ|
ārye daityeśvaraḥ śaṃbhuḥ patnītvena vṛṇoti te|| 63.29||
tasya dānavasiṃhasya jetuḥ śakrasya saṃyuge|
bhavāgryā sarvapatnīnāṃ patnī mṛgavilocane|| 63.30||
evam uktā tadā tena vihasyāhāmareśvarī|
svabāhūnavalokyetthaṃ yuddhaśulkām avehi mām|| 63.31||
māṃ vinirjitya daityo 'asau patnīṃ vai kartum arhati|
mayā vā nihato yātu kākagomāyubhakṣyatām|| 63.32||
evam uktavatīṃ devīm āha mūko hasanniva|
patyā dānavadaityānāṃ kiṃ te yuddhena bhāmini|| 63.33||
kruddhasya yasya samare na śaśāka nirīkṣitum|
mukham airāvataskandhagato 'api balavṛtrahā|| 63.34||
śrutvā tadvacanaṃ tasya prāha devī smayanniva (?)|
tṛṇāni mama daityendrāḥ sarve 'api raṇamūrdhani|| 63.35||
nivedayasva śuṃbhasya gaccha tvaṃ dānavādhama|
dautyenāsi yataḥ prāpto mayāto na vihanyase|| 63.36||
atha praṇamya tāṃ mūko yayau pārśvaṃ suradviṣaḥ|
anujñātaśca tenāsau ākhyātum upacakrame|| 63.37||
sā mayā prārthitā kanyā tvadarthe dānavottama|
uvāca yuddhaśulkāsmi jitvā māṃ netum arhasi|| 63.38||
bhūyaścoktavatī rājan garvam ālambya sāṅganā|
tṛṇāni mama saṃgrāme daityā iti savismayā|| 63.39||
tat tadā vacanaṃ tasyā mūkenoktaṃ niśāmya saḥ|
krodhāddarpācca kāmācca mamṛṣe nāsurottamaḥ|| 63.40||
athotthāya sabhāṃ ramyām agacchaddānavādhipaḥ|
sphāṭikastambhanirvyūhāṃ vicitramaṇitoraṇām|| 63.41||
tasyāṃ siṃhāsane haime svāstīrṇe mahati sthire|
niṣasāda mahābāhuḥ sukhāyāṃ varuṇo yathā|| 63.42||
anu tasya niśuṃbho 'api niṣasāda varāsane|
ratnāṅgadāṃśunivahacchuritoraḥsthalastadā|| 63.43||
tayoranu mahāsattvā viviśurdaityadānavāḥ|
darīṃ himavato ramyāṃ vāriśyāmā ivāmbudāḥ|| 63.44||
atha teṣūpaviṣṭeṣu daityadānavarājasu|
provāca vacanaṃ śumbho ghanastanitanisvanaḥ|| 63.45||
ārakṣiko girau vindhye madīyo mūkadānavaḥ|
vindhyasya śikhare kanyāṃ dṛṣṭavāṃścārurūpiṇīm|| 63.46||
yuddhaśulkāham iti āha madarthe 'anena sārthitā|
tṛṇāni mama daityendrā bhūyaścoktavatī kila|| 63.47||
jitvā tāṃ prasabhaṃ kanyāṃ samare garvaśālinīm|
viceṣṭamānām avaśām adyaivānetum utsahe|| 63.48||
atha tasya vacaḥ śrutvā śaṃbhurnāma mahāsuraḥ|
prahasyoccairmahābāhuridam āhāsureśvaram|| 63.49||
vāmaprakṛtayaḥ sarvāḥ svabhāvena varāṅganāḥ|
parisāntvyāsakṛdrājaṃstāṃ tvam ādātum arhasi|| 63.50||
śrutvātha vacanaṃ śaṃbhormayo dānavasattamaḥ|
provācābhinavotphullanīlanīrajalocanaḥ|| 63.51||
ākāraḥ kaḥ punastasyāḥ kā vā ceṣṭāsurādhipa |
pārśvasthāni ca kānyasyāḥ sadopakaraṇāni vā|| 63.52||
ityuktavati daityendre maye mattebhavikrame|
atha daityapatirmūkaṃ pārśvasthaṃ samacodayat|| 63.53||
yaṃ praśnaṃ pṛṣṭavāṃstatra mayo matimatāṃ varaḥ|
mūkastu taṃ tadā sarvam ākhyātum upacakrame|| 63.54||
sadā susaṃsthitā tryakṣā karāladaśanānanā|
aṣṭabāhurghanaśyāmā sunāsā valgunisvanā|| 63.55||
sārśvasthāni sadā tasyāḥ sarvapraharaṇāni ca|
tanutrāṇi ca mukhyāni citrāṇi ābharaṇāni ca|| 63.56||
atyādityaṃ vapustasyāḥ kāntiścātiniśākarā|
iti ākhyāya tadā mūko vireme daityasaṃsadi|| 63.57||
atha dīrghaṃ viniḥśvasya tadā mayamahāsuraḥ|
provāca sadasi svantaṃ vaco vacanakovidaḥ|| 63.58||
nūnam utpāditā devaiḥ kṛtyā yudhi parājitaiḥ|
vindhyaṃ mahīdhram āyātā vināśāya suradviṣām|| 63.59||
tadalaṃ te tayā rājan santi kanyāḥ sumadhyamāḥ|
dīrghākṣyaścārusarvāṅgyo daityadānavaveśmasu|| 63.60||
samyagāhṛtya tā rājannanurūpāḥ kalasvanāḥ|
yatheṣṭaṃ krīḍa satataṃ prāsādodarasaṃsthitaḥ|| 63.61||
evam ukte tadā vākye mayenāsurasaṃsadi|
prāha vākyaṃ tadā śumbho vihasyetthaṃ mahāsuraḥ|| 63.62||
yadi sā devataiḥ sṛṣṭā kanyā dānavaśāsane|
ahatvā dānavān āśu tadā sā na viraṃsyate|| 63.63||
yāvadeva na kṛtyāsmādabhiyuṃkte kṛtodyamā|
tāvadeva prasahyāśu tāṃ vaśe kartum arhatha|| 63.64||
tato 'anumenire sarve daityadānavasattamāḥ|
vacanaṃ daityarājasya kālenābhipracoditāḥ|| 63.65||
atha sadasi samastān daityasiṃhāṃstadānīṃ tridaśapativijetā vākyam etadvihṛtya|
udapatadavalambisvacchaśubhroruhāro navajalabharanamraḥ prāvṛṣīvāmbuvāhaḥ|| 63.66||
iti skandapurāṇe (mahadara?)saṃvāde
triṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 63.63||

catuḥṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
āhatya bherīḥ sannahya ditijā dānavāśca te|
tadā sannāhayāmāsuu rathanāgaturaṅgamān|| 64.1||
gṛhītatoyān ānīya tato daityā mataṅgajān|
madasphātikarān dattvā dhūpāṃśca kavalāni ca|| 64.2||
tathā kakṣāśca sannāhyā graiveyāṃśca susaṃskṛtān|
aṃkuśān sarvalohāṃśca hemaratnapariṣkṛtān || 64.3||
kareṇuṣu samārūḍhāḥ samantādgajasādinaḥ|
ābabandhurvicitrāṇi varmāṇi vidhivat tadā|| 64.4||
tiryagūrdhvamukhān samyagbabandhustomareṣudhīn|
āyudhāni ca sarvāṇi babandhurubhayorapi|| 64.5||
pārśvayorāsanānāṃ tu trayāṇām api bhāgaśaḥ|
vaijayantīpatākāśca samucchiśriyire tataḥ|| 64.6||
turaṅgān snātapītāṃśca vaṇino baddhabāladhīn|
ārūḍhā baddhanistriṃśā dānavā lohajālinaḥ|| 64.7||
ārūḍhā rathinaḥ kecidrathān yuktaturaṅgamān|
sāyudhān sapatākāṃśca prayastān svakṣakūbarān|| 64.8||
atha śuṃbho niśumbhaśca bhrātarau dānaveśvarau|
āruhya baddhakavacau balonmattau mahāsurau|| 64.9||
sāṃgrāmikau susaṃyattau rathau valgatturaṅgamau|
sāyudhau sapatākau ca kārttasvaramayau pṛthak|| 64.10||
nirjagmaturmahoraskau prayuktajayamaṅgalau|
māgadhairvandibhiḥ sūtaiḥ stūyamānau puraḥsaraiḥ|| 64.11||
tato yātuṃ samārabdhāstūryāṇi āhatya saṃghaśaḥ|
yatrāste kauśikī devī taṃ śailam abhito 'asurāḥ|| 64.12||
atha dānavasiṃhānāṃ dhvajāḥ peturyiyāsatām|
aśivaṃ ca śivā nedurdīptāyāṃ diśi saṃsthitāḥ|| 64.13||
papāta nabhāso reṇuḥ kapotodaradhūsaraḥ|
upariṣṭācca senāyā babhramurgṛdhravāyasāḥ|| 64.14||
pratīpaṃ ca vavau teṣāṃ rajogarbhaḥ samīraṇaḥ|
rarāsa paruṣaṃ vyoma cacāla ca vasundharā|| 64.15||
parājayanimittāni budhyamānāḥ suradviṣaḥ|
abhijagmuḥ kṛtāntena kṛṣyamāṇā ivāvaśāḥ|| 64.16||
ādideśātha daityendro mūkam ārakṣikaṃ tadā|
gṛhāṇa śulkam iti tāṃ brūhi gatvā sumadhyamām|| 64.17||
sa gatvā vacanāt tasya praṇamyovāca kauśikīm|
śulkaṃ kila gṛhāṇārye dīyamānaṃ suradviṣā|| 64.18||
evam astviti sā procya taṃ visṛjya ca dānavam|
vyavardhata mahāyogā yogam āsthāya kauśikī|| 64.19||
atha tasyāḥ samutpedurgātrebhyaḥ pramadottamāḥ|
baddhagodhāṃgulitrāṇāḥ sāyudhā bhīmadarśanāḥ|| 64.20||
vāyasī vāyasāsyānāṃ strīṇāṃ koṭyā samāvṛtā|
upakā kokilāsyābhistāvatībhirmahābalā|| 64.21||
pracaṇḍā siṃhavaktrābhirdevībhirabhisaṃvṛtā|
ugrā vyāghramukhābhiśca paritaḥ parirakṣitā|| 64.22||
jayā ca gajavaktrābhirjayantī ca mahābalā|
devībhiḥ śikhivaktrābhirameyābhirvṛtānaghā|| 64.23||
jayamānā śvavaktrābhirhaṃsyāsyābhiḥ prabhāvṛtā|
prabhāvatī ca cakrāhvavadanābhirmahābalā|| 64.24||
śivā gomāyuvaktrābhiraśivā vidviṣāṃ raṇe|
saramā śvamukhībhiśca vṛtā paramadurjayā|| 64.25||
vijayā śyenavaktrābhiḥ sarvataḥ parirakṣitā|
kaṃkāsyābhirvṛtā mṛtyurhantrībhiḥ samare ripūn|| 64.26||
niyatirmadguvaktrābhirdurjayābhiḥ parairyudhi|
aśaniḥ kukkuṭāsyābhirbahvībhirabhināditā|| 64.27||
revatī vṛṣadaṃśā ca pūtanā kaṭapūtanā|
ālambā kinnarī ṣaṣṭhī śakunirmukhamaṇḍikā|| 64.28||
alakṣmīradhṛtirlakṣmīḥ potakī vānarī spṛhā|
etāścānyāśca kauśikyāḥ saṃbabhūvurmahābalāḥ|| 64.29||
nānāveṣadharābhiśca bahvībhiḥ parito vṛtā|
biṃbhratībhirvicitrāṇi kavacāni āyudhāni ca|| 64.30||
sasarja kauśikī tūrṇaṃ haimān sāṃgrāmikān rathān|
yuktānaśvairmanovegaiḥ sāyudhānucchritadhvajān|| 64.31||
vājinaḥ sopakaraṇān madonmattān mataṅgajān|
āyudhāni tanutrāṇi tūryāṇi vividhāni ca|| 64.32||
uvāca ca mahāyogā tā devīḥ purataḥ sthitāḥ|
devyaḥ śuṃbho niśuṃbhaśca bhrātarau devakaṇṭakau|| 64.33||
netuṃ māṃ kila saṃgrāme vijitya raṇamūrdhani|
āgatau tau balonmattau sahitau daityadānavaiḥ|| 64.34||
tāvahaṃ vinihaṃsyāmi śeṣān hatasuradviṣaḥ|
ajarāścāmarāścaiva bhaviṣyatha mahābalāḥ|| 64.35||
iti tābhyo varaṃ dattvā samādiśya ca tāstadā|
devīrdevī mahābhāgā yuddhāya kṛtaniścayā|| 64.36||
atha sā svarathaṃ mahārathaṃ manasācintayadacyutā tadā|
tam upasthitam āśu cintitaṃ pradadau yaṃ girirājanandanā|| 64.37||
jvaladagnisamānavarcasaṃ parito ratnamayūkhamālinam|
purataḥ samavekṣya kauśikī sukṛtaṃ hemamayaṃ nabhaścaram|| 64.38||
vividhāyudhavarmasaṃyutaṃ pracalatpiṅgasaṭākalāpibhiḥ|
samare jayibhirdviṣadbalaṃ yuktaṃ kesaribhirmahābalaiḥ|| 64.39||
nṛtyanmayūreṇa vikīrṇabhāsā samucchritenātitarāṃ dṛḍhena|
haimena ratnadyutibhāsvareṇa dhvajapravekeṇa virājamānam|| 64.40||
jagrāha vijayā chatraṃ siṃhī sūtā tadābhavat|
jayantī ca jayā cāsyā dadhatuścāmarāṇyatha|| 64.41||
tataḥ sā baddhakavacā vividhāyudhadhāriṇī|
āruroha rathaṃ divyaṃ kṛtāśīrjayamaṅgalā|| 64.42||
saṃpūrṇacandradyutinātha mūrdhni samucchritenātapavāraṇena|
saṃbījyamānā ca vicitradaṇḍaiḥ sucāmarairindumarīcigauraiḥ|| 64.43||
tatastāstūryam āhatya nedurnādān pṛthagvidhān|
devyā devyaḥ susaṃyuktā babhūvuśca purassarāḥ|| 64.44||
tena nādena daityānāṃ hṛdayāni cakampire|
visasarja śakṛnmūtraṃ hastyaśvaṃ cāsure bale|| 64.45||
cakampa iva bhūrlokaścukṣubhuḥ sāgarā iva|
viceluriva śailendrāḥ pūritaṃ va nabhastalam|| 64.46||
tadā taddevatānīkaṃ patākādhvajaśobhitam|
vireje vinadattūryaṃ sitanistriṃśasaṃkulam|| 64.47||
balākāpaṃktiśabalaṃ sendracāpaṃ mahāsvanam|
nabhasye māsi sataḍidvṛndaṃ jalamucām iva|| 64.48||
tato jagāma saṃyacchaddaityendrābhimukhaṃ tadā|
javena devatānīkaṃ saṃkṣipyeva diśo daśa|| 64.49||
atha dadṛśuranīkam āgataṃ suraripavo vividhocchritadhvajam|
pratibhayajananaṃ mahāsvanaṃ pralaya ivāmbudavṛndam unnatam|| 64.50||
iti skandapurāṇe śumbhaniśumbhayuddhe
sainyavarṇanaṃ nāma
catuḥṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 64.61||

pañcaṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha tā devatāḥ kruddhā daityānagrasarāṃstadā|
nijaghnurvividhaiḥ śastraiste ca tā vibhiduryudhi|| 65.1||
daityā nānāyudhopetā devīrjaghnustadā raṇe|
abalā balino vīrāḥ samare 'amaradviṣaḥ|| 65.2||
turaṅginasturaṅgasthāḥ padātīṃśca padātayaḥ|
rathino rathasaṃsthāśca gajasthā gajasādinaḥ|| 65.3||
rathā nāgāsturaṅgāśca rathān nāgāṃsturaṅgamān|
padātīḥ sādinaḥ śūrāḥ sādinīśca padātayaḥ|| 65.4||
devyo 'api yudhi saṃkruddhāḥ pattisādirathadvipān|
nirjaghnurdānavendrāṇāṃ prāsaśaktiparaśvadhaiḥ|| 65.5||
pādaiśca pipiṣuḥ śūrān nipātya bhuvi dānavān|
vibhidurmuṣṭibhiḥ kāścicchirāṃsi suravidviṣām|| 65.6||
vidāryoraḥsthalaṃ kāścit samare darpaśālinām|
papuśca rudhiraṃ devyaḥ prāṇaiḥ saha suradviṣām|| 65.7||
cchināṃśca khaṇḍaśaḥ keciddhetīnutthāya vegitāḥ|
nirjaghnurdevatāḥ kruddhā muṣṭibhirvajrasaṃhataiḥ|| 65.8||
kecinmadāmbuniṣyandaśyāmagaṇḍasthalā gajāḥ|
pipiṣuḥ paramakruddhāḥ samare devatārathān|| 65.9||
kapolabhittisaṃlīnamattaṣaṭpadapaṃktayaḥ|
hatārohā gajāḥ kecinnirjaghnurdaityadevatāḥ|| 65.10||
varmiṇaḥ kecidudbhrāntaśitanistriṃśapāṇayaḥ|
cicchidurdevatānīkaṃ devatā dānavānapi|| 65.11||
mattāḥ praticchinnamukhāṃśca kecidgandhena vijñāya gajān gajendrāḥ|
ghrātvā tu gandhaṃ sahasābhijaghnurādhoraṇairapyabhisaṃgṛhītāḥ|| 65.12||
visphāryamāṇāni mahādhanūṃsi mahābalairdānakyodhamukhyaiḥ|
tāraṃ viresuḥ samarājireṣu krauñcā iva vyomni śaranniśāsu|| 65.13||
tūryasvanairjyātalasannipātairnāgāśvanādai rathanemighoṣaiḥ|
saṃpūrṇakuñjodarakandaro 'asau vindhyaścacāleva tadā samagraḥ|| 65.14||
devyaḥ samutsārya raṇe ripūṇām uccairvineduḥ prasabhaṃ balāni|
neduśca nādān parihṛṣṭacittāḥ protsārya devīryudhi daityayodhāḥ|| 65.15||
balāni kiṃcit kṣatajokṣitāni pracakrire tatra gatāgatāni|
mahāvanānīva samīraṇena samīritānyudgatapallavāni|| 65.16||
chinnāni vaktrāṇi purassarāṇāṃ vicitrahaimābharaṇojjvalāni|
devībhirājau patitāni rejurnikṛttanālāni yathāmbujāni|| 65.17||
pratyāhatā vidrutabhītanāgā sā devatābhirnitahatāśvayodhā|
daityendrasiṃhaiḥ pratisannivṛttairdolāyamāneva camūrbabhūva|| 65.18||
hatā nipetuḥ samare nadanto devadviṣām añjanaśailakalpāḥ|
devībhirābaddhavicitraghaṇṭā marmātigairvāṇavarairgajendrāḥ|| 65.19||
balāni teṣām abhisṛtya vegādabhyāhatāni āśvapaserurājau|
mahodadhiṃ prāpya vivṛddhikāle pratyāhatānīva sarijjalāni|| 65.20||
devyaśca daityāśca mahāsamāje virejire 'anyonyavisaktavāṇāḥ|
saṃsaktabhāsopagame ghanānām abhre samūhā iva tārakāṇām|| 65.21||
udghṛṣya nāmānyatha dānavendrā nirjagmurāśu svabalādrathasthāḥ|
kruddhāḥ suyattā rathināṃ variṣṭhā visphārya citrāṇi śarāsanāni|| 65.22||
devyo 'api saṃyattatarā rathasthāḥ kruddhā javenātha tadābhisasruḥ|
meghasvanaṃ pratyudiyāya ṣaṣṭhī kārtasvaraṃ mṛtyurudīrṇakopā|| 65.23||
drumeṇa lakṣmīratha saṃyugasthā mayena kāntiḥ saramā mureṇa|
ghanena caṇḍā niyatiḥ khareṇa prabhāvatī dhundhumayāt saroṣā|| 65.24||
daityā yuyutsotsukamānasāste devīḥ samāyāḥ sabhujaiḥ saśastraiḥ|
abhyāyayuḥ śīghram amṛṣyamāṇāḥ khyātāvalepāḥ svarathaiḥ suyattāḥ|| 65.25||
jyotiḥprakāśāṃstapanīyapuṃkhān ākarṇapūrṇāyatacāpamuktān|
saṃpreṣayāmāsuradīnasattvā bāṇapravekān yudhi devatānāṃ || 65.26||
devyo 'atha teṣāṃ niśitān supuṃkhān marmacchido dūragamān supatrān|
āgacchatāṃ dānavayūthapānāṃ bāṇānanantān sasṛjustathaiva|| 65.27||
te bāṇamukhyā vividhā virejuranyonyamuktā vyatiṣajyamānāḥ|
te pūrṇamāsyāṃ vighane dinānte bhāsaḥ samūḍhā iva cāndrasaurāḥ|| 65.28||
chinnā nipeturyudhi devatābhirbhujāḥ saśastrā ditijādhipānām|
nirastabhogā nibiḍā bṛhanto nigīrṇajihvā iva pannagendrāḥ|| 65.29||
meghasvanasyātha raṇe tadānīṃ kruddhā śaraughān visasarja ṣaṣṭhī|
āgacchatastānabhitaḥ pṛṣatkaiściccheda daityaḥ śataśo 'antarikṣe|| 65.30||
bāṇānathodvīkṣya tadā nikṛttā/llaghīyaso 'anyān visasarja tūrṇam|
daityo 'api tān āpatataḥ pṛṣatkān vrātaiḥ śarāṇāṃ bahuśaścakartta|| 65.31||
nikṛttya bāṇān ditijaḥ punastāṃścikṣepa ṣaṣṭhyā daśa rukmapuṃkhān|
tān āśu ṣaṣṭhī prativārya daityaṃ vivyādha ṣaṣṭhyā tapanīyapuṃkhaiḥ|| 65.32||
sa tairvibhinno rudhirāktamūrtiḥ pravihvalaḥ kiṃcidavāgbabhūva|
apākarot taṃ samarāt svasūto rathena jāmbūnadacitritena|| 65.33||
kārtasvanaḥ kāñcanacitrapuṃkhān sasarja devyāḥ samare pṛṣatkān|
ciccheda tān mṛtyurudārapuṃkhairanāgatāneva śarāñcharaughaiḥ|| 65.34||
chittvā śarāṃstasya śarairvicitrairvivyādha taṃ vakṣasi pañcaṣaṣṭhyā|
bhinnaḥ sa tairāśu tathā vireje vyamnyarkapādairiva vārivāhaḥ|| 65.35||
aśvāṃśca tasyāśu jaghāna mṛtyuḥ pṛthak pṛṣatkaistapanīyapuṃkhaiḥ|
āplutya taityo 'atha rathāddhatāśvāt pragṛhya carmāsivaraṃ ca dhautam|| 65.36||
kruddho nitāntāyataraktanetro vegena devīm abhitaḥ sasāra|
taccarma tasyāpatataḥ śaraughaiścakartta mṛtyuḥ śataśaḥ śitāgraiḥ|| 65.37||
sa kṛttacarmāvaraṇaḥ surendro nistriṃśam udyamya niśātadhāram|
abhyadravanmṛtyum abhūt tadānīṃ khe rohiṇīṃ megha ivābhividyut|| 65.38||
tam āpatantaṃ yudhi kālakalpaṃ mṛtyuḥ śarairugrabhujaṅgakalpaiḥ|
jaghāna marmasvabhilakṣiteṣu vyayojayaccāsubhirenam āśu|| 65.39||
lakṣmīrdrumaṃ bāṇavarairajayyā samākiradvāraṇarājalīlam|
karṇāntamuktairniśitairajihmai raṇājire cārusuvarṇapuṃkhaiḥ|| 65.40||
ajihmagāste vividhāḥ supatritā drumasya gātreṣu nipeturāhave|
sa tairvicitraiḥ śuśubhe viṣaktairmahādrumaḥ pakṣigaṇerivāśriteḥ|| 65.41||
lakṣmīṃ tataḥ kiṃpuruṣādhipo 'asau vivyādha vrāṇairdaśabhiḥ supuṃkhaiḥ|
vaktre sa pūrṇendusamānavaktrāṃ bāhvoḥ pṛthak cāṣṭaśatena dhīraḥ|| 65.42||
acintayantīṣu varān varāsyā mukhe 'asya tīkṣṇān nicakhāna bāṇān|
anyānasaṃkhyāṃśca pṛthak śarīre supatritān hāṭakamṛṣṭapuṃkhān|| 65.43||
lakṣmyāstato daityapatiḥ śitena bhallena ciccheda rathe dhvajāgram|
aśvāṃśca tasyāścaturaścaturbhiḥ sūtaṃ ca vivyādha śareṇa tūrṇam|| 65.44||
nārācam ādāya tato 'asya lakṣmīrjaghāna sūtaṃ yudhi devaśatroḥ|
vivyādha vāhāṃśca pṛthak pṛṣatkairdhvajaṃ ca ciccheda rathasya tūrṇam|| 65.45||
yantrā vinā tasya rathaṃ tadānīṃ te sāyakairapratimaiḥ prataptāḥ|
saṃgrāmabhūmerapaninyuraśvāḥ prāṇāniva svān parirakṣamāṇāḥ|| 65.46||
kāntirmayaṃ bāṇaśatairavākiranmayaḥ Ca kāntiṃ niśitaiḥ śaraughaiḥ|
nīhārapātairiva sāndhakāraṃ tadā tayorantaram āsa tatra|| 65.47||
ādānasandhānavikarṣaṇeṣu sthānakramapragrahatejaneṣu|
śikṣāguṇaistāvaparaspareṇa viśeṣayāmāsaturājimadhye|| 65.48||
kāntirmayāstān nicakarta bāṇān mayaśca kāntyā viśikhān visṛṣṭān|
chidraṃ samāsedaturapradhṛṣyau kiṃcinna tau yatra prasparasya|| 65.49||
aśveṣu sūte sarathe dhvaje ca sarveṣu gātrāvayaveṣu sāsya|
ajihmagān hāṭakamṛṣṭapuṃkhān mayasya kāntirnicakhāna bāṇān|| 65.50||
mayaśca kāntiṃ sarathāṃ sasūtāṃ sacārucitradhvajavājimukhyām|
saṃcchādayāmāsa śitaiḥ pṛṣatkairvanasthalīṃ megha ivāmbuvarṣaiḥ|| 65.51||
kruddhātha kāntiḥ samare mayasya nārācamukhyena supatritena|
sūtaṃ jaghānāśu ripostadānīm aṣṭābhiraṣṭau turagāṃśca bāṇaiḥ|| 65.52||
hatāśvasūto viratho mayo 'atha nistriṃśam ādāya niśātadhāram|
jñātvaiva kāntyāḥ samare prabhāvaṃ vihāya yuddhaṃ viyudutpapāta|| 65.53||
vivyādha tīkṣṇaiḥ saramā raṇājire bāṇairmuraṃ dānavadaityayūthapam|
daityo 'api bāṇaiḥ saramām ajihmagairabhyāhanadgṛdhramayūrapatribhiḥ|| 65.54||
kruddhātha devī niśitena tasya ciccheda bhallena dhanurvicitram|
anyaddhanuḥ so 'atha tadā gṛhītvā vivyādha devyāścaturasturaṅgān|| 65.55||
te vihvalāḥ śoṇitam udvamanto daityendrabāṇābhihatāsturaṅgāḥ|
bhūmau nipetuḥ samare śvasantaḥ prāṇāñjahuścāśu samaṃ samastāḥ|| 65.56||
kruddhātha devī saramāsurasya nistriṃśam udyamya supītadhāram|
utpatya khaṃ tasya tadā jaghāna yantāram aśvāṃśca mahāpramāṇān|| 65.57||
muro 'atha vegena tadāntarikṣam utpatya kopānnihatāśvasūtaḥ|
vivyādha devīṃ daśabhiḥ sutīkṣṇaiḥ śarairurasyugrabhujaṅgakalpaiḥ|| 65.58||
acintayitvā saramā śarāṃstān dhanurviciccheda tadā murasya|
sa kṛrttadhanvā viyatīndraśatrurantardadhe saṃyugam āśu hitvā|| 65.59||
vivyādha caṇḍā ghanam āpatantaṃ śaraiḥ śitāgrairyudhi rukmapuṃkaiḥ|
viddhaḥ sa tairdaityapatirbabhāse karairivendorasitaḥ payodaḥ|| 65.60||
abhyadravat tānavicintya vāṇāṃścaṇḍāṃ ghanaḥ sāyakajālavarṣī|
āgacchatastasya śaraiḥ supatrairvivyādha caṇḍā rathavājimukhyān|| 65.61||
ciccheda daityo 'api samucchritāgraṃ dhvajaṃ turaṅgāṃśca jaghāna devyāḥ|
hitvā rathau tāvavatīrya bhūmau gṛhītacarmāsivarau prayattau|| 65.62||
viceraturmaṇḍalam ājimadhye bhūmiṃ tadāgrāṅgulibhiḥ spṛśantau|
tāṃstāṃśca mārgā/llaghupādacārau chidraṃ na cānyonyam avāpatustau|| 65.63||
abhiplutoccaplutasiṃhapātān nivṛttakākrīḍitakordhvabāhūn|
khagāpayātābhihatāpayātān niṣaṇṇakāviddhaśirobhighātān|| 65.64||
utplutya vegena tathātha tasya śirodharām āśu cakarta caṇḍā|
sa kṛttamūrdhā nipapāta tasyāṃ saṃgrāmabhūmāvurasā "āśu daityaḥ|| 65.65||
sa śoṇitādigdhavapustadānīṃ ghanaḥ parāsuḥ patito dharaṇyām|
rarāja sandhyācchuritorurmūrttirviyadgato nīla ivāmbuvāhaḥ|| 65.66||
vivyādha tīkṣṇairniryatiḥ supatraiḥ kharaṃ śarairvakṣasi hemapuṃkhaiḥ|
āyodhane saṃmukham āpatantaṃ bhallena cāsya dhvajam uccakarta|| 65.67||
viddhaḥ sa tairabhyapatan saroṣo devīṃ jighāṃsuḥ samare 'arihantā|
gurvī gadāṃ cāśu tadā gṛhītvā cikṣepa devyā rudhirāktamūrttiḥ|| 65.68||
sā dānavāgryeṇa gadā pramuktā vicitrahemojjvalacārughaṇṭā|
saṃcūrṇayāmāsa rathaṃ niyatyāḥ sūtaṃ dhvajaṃ cāśu samucchritāgram|| 65.69||
utpatya tūrṇaṃ niyatiḥ svavāhāt krodhena saṃraktavilolanetrā|
abhyetya taṃ dānavayodhamukhyaṃ khaḍgena madhye 'asya śiras paphāla|| 65.70||
sa dānavo visphuṭitottamāṅgaḥ kṣitau vireje srutaraktadhāraḥ|
vajreṇa bhinnaḥ śikharāgradeśe giriryathā dhāturasapravāhī|| 65.71||
prabhāvatī dhundhum ajihmayātaiḥ śilīmukhairabhyahanat supatraiḥ|
urasyudārā daśabhiḥ śitāgrairghanāghanavrātasamānavarṇaiḥ|| 65.72||
jaghāna sā ṣoḍaśa devatāresturaṅgamān ṣoḍaśabhiḥ pṛṣatkaiḥ|
nihatya caikena rathe 'asya sūtam ekena cāsya dhvajam uccakarta|| 65.73||
dhundhurgadāṃ bhārasahasragurvīṃ cikṣepa kārtasvaracārughaṇṭām|
tām āpatantīṃ śataśaścakartta prabhāvatī daityapatipramuktām|| 65.74||
ādāya daityaḥ parighaṃ mahāntam āplutya vāhādabhitaḥ sasāra|
devīm asāvañjanaśailanīlo raṇājire kāla ivāttadaṇḍaḥ|| 65.75||
abhyāpatantaṃ yudhi dānavendraṃ devī śarairabhyahanat supatraiḥ|
devyā samastānavicintya bāṇānabhyetya tām āhavamūrdhni roṣāt|| 65.76||
udbhrāmya vaivasvatadaṇḍakalpaṃ lauhaṃ prayastaṃ parighorubāhuḥ|
nyapātayat taṃ parighaṃ rathe 'asyā girernitambe kuliśaṃ yathendraḥ|| 65.77||
acūrṇayat taṃ ratham āśu devyāḥ sāśvaṃ sasūtadhvajahemacakram|
kālāyaso 'asau parigho 'asurāsto vegena tatrāpasasāra devī|| 65.78||
dṛṣṭvā sa tāṃ tatra tadāpayātāṃ tam eva lauhaṃ parighaṃ gṛhītvā|
abhyadravaddānavayodhamukhyo divīva citrām asitaḥ payodaḥ|| 65.79||
utpatya sā divyavarāstramuktaiḥ kṣurapramukhyaiḥ parighaṃ cakarta|
udyamya muṣṭiṃ nibiḍaṃ tato 'asyā bhūyo 'atha daityo viyadutpapāta|| 65.80||
taṃ marmagairmarmasu bāṇamukhyaiḥ saṃtāḍayaddānavam āśu devī|
bhinnaḥ sa tairmarmagamaiḥ supuṃkhairantardadhe dānavayodhamukhyaḥ|| 65.81||
atha samaram apāsya yodhamukhyairvihataparākramapauruṣairapetaiḥ|
surapatiripavo vinadya nādān dviradavarānadhitasthurāttaśastrāḥ|| 65.82||
iti skandapurāṇe śumbhaniśumbhasaṃgrāme
devīyuddhāṃ nāma
pañcaṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 65.65||

ṣaṭṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
devyo 'api teṣāṃ viditaprayatnā gajottamān āruruhuḥ sayatnāḥ|
śucīn madāmbusravataḥ sudantān praśastagātrāmbarahastapakṣān (?)|| 66.1||
supuṣkarānunnatavṛttakumbhān subāladhīnañcitacārukarṇān|
sudantaveṣṭān kalaviṅkanetrān suvakṣasaḥ svāsanapṛṣṭhavaṃśān|| 66.2||
sāṅgrāmikānagrajavān vayaḥsthān suśikṣitānunnatapūrvakāyān|
ābaddhavarmāyudhacitraghaṇṭān samucchritorudhvajavaijayantīn|| 66.3||
tāsāṃ patākādhvajaśobhitāni vicitranānāyudhabhūṣaṇāni|
mātaṅgavṛndāni tadā babhūvurvane vanānīva samāgatāni|| 66.4||
daityāpi te vāraṇamūrdhni ṣannā visphārayanto vibabhurdhanūṃṣi|
sendrāyudhāḥ sāśaniśabdagarbhāḥ śaileṣu meghā iva sannilīnāḥ|| 66.5||
sainyāni tāni āhanane gajānām ādhoraṇairāśvabhicoditāni|
anyonyam āpeturabhīritāni vātena vṛndāni yathā ghanānām|| 66.6||
vegena nāgānabhisṛtya nāgā madānmadaśyāmamukhān viṣāṇaiḥ|
lohābhinaddhairvisakāṇḍagauraiḥ śambūkadeśeṣvabhijaghnurājau|| 66.7||
prasārya hastānabhitaśca keciddānānugandhaṃ dviradābheseruḥ|
ādhoraṇairaṅkuśapāśavāgbhiravidhyamānāpi madābhidṛptāḥ|| 66.8||
chinnāni peturniśitaiḥ kṣurapraiḥ samucchritāni ātapavāraṇāni|
citrāḥ patākā vividhā dhvajāśca paraspareṇāhanane gajebhyaḥ|| 66.9||
yodhā nipetuḥ pariniṣṭananto viddhāḥ śarairmarmasu devatābhiḥ|
saphenam āsyai rudhiraṃ vamanto dhanūṃṣi sajjāni karairdadhānāḥ|| 66.10||
nāgo nipetuḥ parito 'abhipadya marmātigairbāṇavarairvibhinnāḥ|
devībhirājau ditijādhipānāṃ vātābhinunnā iva gaṇḍaśailāḥ|| 66.11||
mātaṅgamukhyān patitān parāsūn raṇājire nīlagirīndrakalpān |
gandhena nāgāḥ samadāḥ parītya vinamya kecidvadanairvineduḥ|| 66.12||
chinnāni vaktrāṇi sakuṇḍalāni bhujāḥ saśtrāśca sucandanāktāḥ|
peturgajebhyo 'asurayūthapānāṃ devībhirājau niśitaiḥ kṣurapraiḥ|| 66.13||
cukūjuruccaiḥ parito dhanūṃṣi vinedurāhatya surārimukhyāḥ|
vipusphururjyāḥ parikṛṣya muktāḥ śarābhividdhāśca gajā niṣeduḥ|| 66.14||
nāgaiḥ patadbhirviśikhābhividdhaiḥ samucchritorudhvajacārupṛṣṭhaiḥ|
āstīryate bhūranilapranunnaiḥ satālavṛkṣairiva śailapādaiḥ|| 66.15||
nāgā gajān āhanane 'abhijaghnurdaityāśca devīrditijāṃśca devyaḥ|
daityān gajendrā dviradāṃśca daityāḥ kruddhāḥ saroṣānabhisṛtya tatra|| 66.16||
śastrābhitaptaiḥ patitaiḥ samantānmātaṅgavṛndairgirisānukalpaiḥ|
saṃcārayogyā na babhūva bhūmirāyoghane daivatadānavānām|| 66.17||
abhyarditāni svabalāni dṛṣṭvā devībhirājau nihatadvipāni|
śumbho niśumbhaśca samājabhūmim ājagmaturdaityapatī rathasthau|| 66.18||
agresaraiḥ pattituraṅganāgairvrātaiśca devadviṣatām upetau|
visphārayantau dhanuṣī vicitre yuddhāya yattau parighorubāhū|| 66.19||
jñātvā tayorāgamanaṃ tadānīṃ devī calatpiṅgalakeśarāḍhyāt|
saṃcodayāmāsa rathasya siṃhān visphārayantī samare dhanūṃṣi|| 66.20||
jyāniṃ javasyātha turaṅgamāṇāṃ madapramoṣaṃ ca mahādvipānām|
cetovimohaṃ suravidviṣāṃ ca cāpasvanenaiva cakāra devī|| 66.21||
ājau samāsthāya paraṃ prayatnaṃ śarāḥ surāṇāṃ ripubhiḥ samastāḥ|
aprāpya devīṃ patitāḥ pṛthivyāṃ parājayaṃ prāhurivāsurāṇām|| 66.22||
gabhastibhiḥ sthāvarajaṅgamāni vyāpnoti yadvat savitā dineṣu|
tadvaccharaughairditijādhipānāṃ raṇājire vyāpa balāni devī|| 66.23||
nipeturāśu vyasavasturaṅgamā vicaskhalurmattagajāḥ kṣaranmadāḥ|
cakampire yodhavarāḥ suradviṣāṃ samaṃ samastāḥ samare śarāhatāḥ|| 66.24||
arcirbhiriddhairjvalito yathānalaḥ kakṣāṇi śuṣkāṇi dahatyavāritaḥ|
dīptaiḥ śaraughaiḥ samare 'amaradviṣāṃ sainyāni tadvat pradadāha kauśikī|| 66.25||
chāyāṃ yathā sthāvarajaṃgamānāṃ madhyandine 'alpāṃ kurute vivasvān|
devī tathā tāṃ dhvajinīṃ ripūṇām alpāvaśiṣṭāṃ samare cakāra|| 66.26||
āhūya devīm atha dānavādhipau visphārya cāpe mahatī bhiseratuḥ|
tīkṣṇaiḥ supatrairviśikhaiśca kauśikīṃ saṃchādayāmāsaturāhavājire|| 66.27||
cāpeṣu yattau hariṣu dhvajeṣu mahābhujau krodhaparītacittau|
daityeśvarau saṃyati devatāyā nicakhnaturvāṇavarān supatrān|| 66.28||
daiteśvarāstānatha sāyakaughānacintayitvā ripudarpahantrī|
vivyādha daityau yudhi rukmapuṅkhaiḥ suparvabhirvāṇavaraiḥ supatraiḥ|| 66.29||
daityāvapīṣūnavicintya śūrau gade pragṛhyojjvalacārughaṇṭe|
udbhrāmya yatnātiśayena devyā raṇājire cikṣipaturbṛhatyau|| 66.30||
te vyomni bāṇaiḥ śataśo nikṛtya suparvabhirhāṭakacārupuṃkhaiḥ|
viccheda devī kavace vicitre tayoḥ kṣuraprairaparaiḥ śitāgraiḥ|| 66.31||
jaghāna cāśvānatha sārathī ca dhvajau ca citrau rathayoścakartta|
cakhāna cānyānapi satpṛṣatkān suradviṣormarmasu hemapuṃkhān|| 66.32||
śuṃbho niśuṃbhaśca rathāvapāsya daityeśvarau bāṇavarābhitaptau|
ādāya nistriṃśavarau tadānīm utpetaturvyoma śitāsinīlam|| 66.33||
atha nabhasi vimeghe dhautanistriṃśanīle drutataram abhisṛtya grīvayoḥ sampragṛhya|
dititanayapatī tau niṣpipeṣāśu devī vigatabhayaviṣādaiḥ stūyamānā munīndraiḥ|| 66.34||
asṛgatha vadanābhyām udvamantau saphenaṃ sapadi vihatavīryau piṣṭasarvāṅgasandhī|
asubhirapagataistau raktaparyantanetrau kṣititalam abhitastau petaturdaityasiṃhau|| 66.35||
iti skandapurāṇe śumbhaniśumbhanipātanaṃ nāma
ṣaṭṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 66.66||

saptaṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ājagmuḥ kauśikīṃ draṣṭum atha vindhyaṃ divaukasaḥ|
ādityā vasavo rudrā marutvān maruto 'aśvinau|| 67.1||
dharmāṅgirośano dakṣavasiṣṭhabhṛgukaśyapāḥ|
pulastyapulahāgastyasanakrātrisanandanāḥ|| 67.2||
apsaroyakṣagandharvāḥ siddhā nāgā mahoragāḥ|
upavedāśca yajñāśca vedā vidyāḥ sarasvatī|| 67.3||
samudrāḥ saritaḥ śailāstīrthāni vividhāni ca|
mātaro lokapālāśca nakṣatrāṇi dhruvo grahāḥ|| 67.4||
athocurdevatā devīṃ dyutimatyo mahādyutim|
prahṛṣṭā hṛṣṭamanasām āsīnām asuradviṣaḥ|| 67.5||
dānavendrau mahāsattvau tvayā trailokyakaṇṭakau|
nighnatyā devi lokānāṃ duḥkhaśalyam apākṛtam|| 67.6||
ṛṣayaḥ pāvanaṃ devi havirjuhvati sāmpratam|
chandāṃsyadhīyate coccairācaranti vratāni ca|| 67.7||
yajño 'ayam adhunā viprairijyate bahudakṣiṇaḥ|
uṭajeṣu ca viśvastā munayaḥ śerate sukham|| 67.8||
āsate nirbhayā devi santaḥ sanmārgam āśritāḥ|
āvirbhūtaḥ punarloke vichinnaḥ satkriyāpathaḥ|| 67.9||
lokapālāḥ śirāṃsyuccaistvatprasādācca bibhrati|
pṛktaḥ puṣparajobhiśca sukho vāti samīraṇaḥ|| 67.10||
jalāni devi saritaḥ svacchāni śiśirāṇi ca|
tvatprasādānmahāyoge vahanti vigataklamāḥ|| 67.11||
idānīṃ ca punarjātā girayo girijātmaje|
vijvarāḥ śiśirasvādunirjharodakavāhinaḥ|| 67.12||
phaṇān svastikacakrāṅkānuccairdadhati bhoginaḥ|
udanvantaśca viśvāsādidānīṃ sukham āsate|| 67.13||
bhramantyapsaraso devi tvatprasādācca sāṃpratam|
saccetovimale vyomni vilāsālasalocanāḥ|| 67.14||
siddhāṅganāśca sevante viśvastā devi sāṃpratam|
śikhareṣu mahīdhrāṇām utphullāṃścandanadrumān|| 67.15||
svabhāvānmadhupānācca raktotpalavilocanāḥ|
vicarantyadhunā yakṣā gandhamādanasānuṣu|| 67.16||
sukhaṃ bibharti vasudhām idānīṃ vigataklamaḥ|
śeṣaḥ phaṇaiḥ svaratnāṃśuvitānapariveṣibhiḥ|| 67.17||
mātā tvam asi lokānāṃ bhītānām abhayapradā|
vṛṇu devi varāniṣṭānabhiṣicyasva cācyute|| 67.18||
evam uktā surairdevī prāha kiṃcit smayanniva|
icchāmi pitaraṃ draṣṭum asamagrendumaulinam|| 67.19||
suprasannaṃ prasannāṃ ca jananīṃ ca śailanandanām|
pitṛbhyāṃ cāpyanujñātām abhiṣekṣyatha māṃ tataḥ|| 67.20||
evam uktāḥ surā dadhyuravyagramanasastadā|
sapatnīkaṃ mahādevam amitadyutipauruṣam|| 67.21||
atha te dadṛśurdevā devadevam umāpatim|
tejasām iva sarveṣāṃ saṃghātaṃ purataḥ sthitam|| 67.22||
jaṭānāṃ prāntababhrūṇāṃ śirasā bhāram unnatam|
bibhrāṇaṃ jvalitaṃ vahniṃ dīptānām arciṣām iva|| 67.23||
karpūrabhaṅgagaureṇa snānaṃ puṇyena bhasmanā|
prāntahemalatājālaṃ raupyaṃ girim ivocchritam|| 67.24||
tejasā svena tejāṃsi tirayantaṃ divaukasām|
madhyandine pradīpānām arcīṃsīva divākaram|| 67.25||
sudhāmbusyandinīṃ tanvīm ekataḥ pariveṣiṇīm|
dadhānaṃ maulinā kiṃcit kuṭilām aindavīṃ kalām|| 67.26||
vijihmām ujjvalāṃ gurvīṃ dhūsarāṃ bhasmareṇunā|
saiṃhīṃ vasānam ālambām īṣadbhaṅgavatīṃ tvacam|| 67.27||
churitopāntakāyena phaṇaratnamarīcibhiḥ|
mahatā bhogapatinā vakṣaḥsthalavisarpiṇā|| 67.28||
bhavānīṃ cāsya pārśvasthāṃ dīpyamānāṃ svatejasā|
vasānām aṃśukaṃ raktaṃ kalpapādapasambhavam|| 67.29||
mandāramālām utphullāṃ mattālikulasevitām|
dadhānām uttamāṅgena svareṇūtkarapiñjarām|| 67.30||
svaḥśilpighaṭitaiścitrai ratnāṃśupariveṣibhiḥ|
śātakuṃbhamayaiḥ ślāghyairbhūṣitāṃ bhūṣaṇottamaiḥ|| 67.31||
bibhratīṃ rucirāṃ śuddhāṃ śaraccandrāṃśunirmalām|
śirodhareṇāmahatīm ekāvalim anuttamām|| 67.32||
athotthāya surāḥ sarve kauśikī cānatānanā|
tayoścaraṇapadmeṣu nipetustuṣṭamānasāḥ|| 67.33||
athodvīkṣya mahādevaḥ kauśikīm idam abravīt|
ajeyā sarvabhūtānāṃ mahāyogā mahādyutiḥ|| 67.34||
vicariṣyasi lokāṃstvaṃ sarvatrāpratighātinī|
imāśca devatāḥ sarvāstvatprasādādanindite|| 67.35||
bhaktyā balyupahāraścaiva pūjayiṣyanti mānavāḥ|
varadā cāpi bhaktānāṃ bhaviṣyasi sadānaghe|| 67.36||
abhiṣicyasva ca kṣipraṃ surairasurasūdani|
kṛtsnaṃ rakṣa ca bhūrlokaṃ pūjyamānā sadāvyaye|| 67.37||
śarvāṇī ca pariṣvajya mūrdhni cāghrāya kauśikīm|
prāha prītā mahābhāgā matprabhāvādbhaviṣyasi|| 67.38||
arcayanti yathā māṃ ca surā yakṣā mahoragāḥ|
gandharvā munayaḥ siddhāstathā tvām apyanindite|| 67.39||
arcayiṣyanti sarvatra bhaktāḥ stosyanti cāvyaye|
evaṃ tasmai varaṃ dattvā girijāvṛṣabhadhvajau|| 67.40||
namaskṛtau tadā devairantardadhaturavyayau|
athendro viśvakarmāṇām ādideśa tadā prabhuḥ|| 67.41||
sudharmeva sabhā divyā kriyatām iha sāmpratam|
ṛtūṃśca sarvāṃstatrettham ādideśa śatakratuḥ|| 67.42||
nānāpuṣpotkaraiḥ kṣipraṃ bhūmiḥ samyagvibhūṣyatām|
kṣupagulmalatāvṛkṣapuṣpareṇusugandhayaḥ|| 67.43||
ākṣipanto manāṃsyatra sukhā vāntu samīraṇāḥ|
siñcantu vāribhiḥ puṇyairvindhyaprasthaṃ payomucaḥ|| 67.44||
tāraṃ nadantu śikhinaḥ prahṛṣṭāḥ sarvatodiśam|
nṛtyantu paritaścitrān darśayantaḥ pṛthagvidhān|| 67.45||
rasān bhāvān vilāsāṃśca sarve 'apyapsarasāṃ gaṇāḥ|
pratisāryā suvīṇāśca gandharvā madhurasvaram|| 67.46||
layatālasamaṃ geyaṃ gāyantu ca samantataḥ|
āhanyatāṃ samantācca devadundubhayo bhṛśam|| 67.47||
pāṇibhiḥ kaṭhinaistūrṇaṃ citrarūpā mahāsvanāḥ|
mandānilasamuddhūtā līnālikulapaṃktayaḥ 48||
patantvasmin pradeśe ca divyāḥ kusumavṛṣṭayaḥ|
ucchriyantāṃ samantācca patākāścitramūrtayaḥ|| 67.49||
dhvajāśca vividhākārā hemadaṇḍāḥ susaṃskṛtāḥ|
athāśu nirmame tatra viśvakarmā mahādyutiḥ|| 67.50||
nānāratnojjvalastambhāṃ vicitramaṇivedikām|
vajrasphaṭikaniryūhāṃ jāmbūnadamayīṃ śubhām|| 67.51||
indranīlorusopānāṃ muktādāmāvalambinīm|
sadhvajāṃ sapatākāṃ ca ghaṇṭāsvananināditām|| 67.52||
taponiyamayajñānāṃ sākṣāt siddhim ivodgatām|
bhinnakālāni puṣpāṇi dadṛśurdevatāstadā|| 67.53||
samaṃ supuṇyagandhīni vicitrāṇi bahūni ca|
puṣpakiñjalkagarbhāśca sukhasparśāḥ sugandhayaḥ|| 67.54||
nādayanto muhurghaṇṭā vavustatra samīraṇāḥ|
prajaguḥ suragandharvā nanṛtuścāpsarogaṇāḥ|| 67.55||
ṛṣayastuṣṭuvurgībhiḥ puṇyābhiḥ kauśikīṃ tadā|
sarvaratnauṣadhairgandhaiḥ pūrṇāḥ puṇyaiśca vāribhiḥ|| 67.56||
ānītāstatra kalaśā hemaratnamayāḥ śubhāḥ|
padmarāgamayaiḥ siṃhaiścaturbhirvajrakeśaraiḥ|| 67.57||
ucchvasadbhiriva śrīmaduhyamānaṃ hiraṇmayam|
sarvaratnaprabhājālakhacitopāntamaṇḍalam|| 67.58||
kalpayāmāsa devyāśca viśvakarmā varāsanam|
stutibhirjayaśabdaiśca stūyamānā samantataḥ|| 67.59||
ṛṣibhirdevatābhiśca devadevasutā tataḥ|
tasmin siṃhāsane divye niṣasādātha kauśikī|| 67.60||
kṛtasvastyayanā vipraiḥ suhute jātavedasi|
vasānā vāsasī śukle kalpadrumasamudbhave|| 67.61||
muktādāmāvabaddhāṅgī śuklasraganulepanā|
tataḥ saptarṣayo viṣṇurdharmo yajñaḥ prajāpatiḥ|| 67.62||
ādityāḥ kaśyapo rudrā lokapālā hutāśanāḥ|
pṛthivī gaṅgā candramā maruto 'aśvinau|| 67.63||
samudrā vasavo lakṣmīḥ sandhyā kīrtiḥ sarasvatī|
nāgendrā vihageśāśca vividhāśca saridvarāḥ|| 67.64||
ādāya kalaśān sarvānabhyaṣiñcanta kauśikīm|
pūrṇendubimbapratimaṃ ratnadaṇḍaṃ mahādyutim|| 67.65||
jagrāha vitataṃ chatraṃ svayam eva śatakratuḥ|
cāmarairhemadaṇḍaiśca dīrghaiścandrāṃśunirmalaiḥ|| 67.66||
bījayāmāsurāyastairlokapālāstadāvyayām|
uvāca sa tataḥ śrīmān kauśikīṃ pākaśāsanaḥ|| 67.67||
pāhi kṛtsnāṃ bhuvaṃ devo bhaginī tvaṃ mamāvyaye|
bhaktānanugṛhāṇeśe jahi cāmarakaṇṭakān|
vicarasva samastāṃśca lokān siddhagaṇārcitā|| 67.68||
iti vacanam athoktvā kauśikīṃ devarājastridaśagaṇasametaḥ śubhraloloruhāraḥ|
udapatadatha vindhyādvikṣipan vyomni nīlān salilabharavinmrānambuvāhān samantān|| 67.69||
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyānnityaṃ paṭhedvā satsamāgame|
iha loke sukhaṃ prāpya sa yāti paramāṃ gatim|| 67.70||
iti skandapurāṇe kauśikyabhiṣeko nāma
saptaṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 67.67||

aṣṭaṣaṣṭitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha tā devatā devī kauśikī dehasaṃbhavāḥ|
nyaveśayanmahābhāgā deśeṣu nagareṣu ca|| 68.1||
bahuputrāṃ pralambāṃ ca laṅkāyāṃ sannyaveśayat|
lambauṣṭhīṃ vṛṣadaṃśāṃ ca kinnarīṃ caiva siṃhale|| 68.2||
gokarṇe revatīṃ devīṃ pāṇḍyeṣu mukhamaṇḍikām|
ābhīreṣvaśivāṃ caiva śāntiṃ ca varaṇātaṭe|| 68.3||
vatsagulme prabhāṃ devīṃ lakṣmīṃ kolagirāvapi|
upakāṃ pārasīkeṣu vāyasīṃ yavaneṣu ca|| 68.4||
pracaṇḍāṃ ca tuṣāreṣu kośaleṣu ca lambikām|
jayāṃ ca vijayāṃ caiva svapure saṃnyaveśayat|| 68.5||
prabhāvatīṃ kaliṅgeṣu jayantīṃ nāgasāhvaye|
kāśmīreṣu ca sā ṣaṣṭhīṃ saramāṃ malayeṣu ca|| 68.6||
pūtanāṃ ca supīreṣu mṛtyuṃ pṛṣṭapure tathā|
koṭīvarṣe bāhumāṃsāṃ pauṇḍreṣu kaṭapūtanām|| 68.7||
aspṛṣṭāṃ madhyadeśe tu kinnarīṃ barbareṣu ca|
vārāṇasyāṃ nirāyāsyāṃ ccitraghaṇṭāṃ ca kauśikīm|| 68.8||
mahākālīṃ mahākāle vānarīṃ śabareṣu ca|
śeṣāśca devatāḥ sarvā grāmeṣu nagareṣu ca|| 68.9||
karvaṭeṣu mahīdhreṣu kauśikī saṃnyaveśayat|
kasyacit tvatha kālasya svarṇākṣe hi mahātapāḥ|| 68.10||
yatra viṣṇurvaraṃ lebhe devam ārādhya śaṅkaram|
cakraṃ sudarśanaṃ nāma dviṣatām antakopamam|| 68.11||
ṛṣirāste mahābhāgaḥ śaradvān nāma gautamaḥ|
tasya yajñaṃ jagāmātha devī tena nimantritā|| 68.12||
tasyāstatrāgamaṃ jñātvā sūnuḥ śumbhasya vīryavān|
ājagāmāśu taṃ deśaṃ mahiṣo nāma dānavaḥ|| 68.13||
susaṃhataḥ pṛthūrasko mahāgrīvaḥ subāladhiḥ|
vakraśṛṅgaḥ pṛthukhuro viśālocchritamastakaḥ|| 68.14||
baddhavairāśayaḥ krūro mahāsattvo 'atidurjayaḥ|
vajraniṣpeṣaparuṣaṃ nardamāno mahāsvanaḥ|| 68.15||
añjanādrisamaprakhyo yuyutsurbaladarpitaḥ|
devyāḥ panthānam āvarya dānavendrasutaḥ sthitaḥ|| 68.16||
vijñāya tasyāgamanaṃ yogeśā vindhyavāsinī|
jagāma tvaritā tatra yatrāsau dānavādhamaḥ|| 68.17||
atha dṛṣṭvā sa tāṃ devīṃ krodhādraktatarekṣaṇaḥ|
abhyājagāma vegena yatnam āsthāya dānavaḥ|| 68.18||
udbāladhistīkṣṇaviṣāṇakoṭiḥ supīnavakṣāḥ kaṭhinordhvakarṇaḥ|
abhyāpatadguggulatāmranetro javena devīm asitādrikalpaḥ|| 68.19||
taṃ kauśikī vīkṣya tadāpatantaṃ daityendraputraṃ mahiṣaṃ saroṣam|
cukrodha tāmrāyatacārunetrā sthitā dharaṇyām asurendrahantrī|| 68.20||
abhyetya tāṃ dānavarājasūnurbalena mattaḥ parameṇa devīm|
abhyāhanadvakṣasi lolahāre śṛṅgeṇa śakrāyudhakarkaśena|| 68.21||
viṣahya taṃ tasya tadā prahāraṃ jagrāha śṛṅge mahiṣaṃ kareṇa|
udbhrāmya coccaiḥ paritaḥ saroṣā nyapātayadbhūmitale śvasantam|| 68.22||
udgṛhya sā bāladhim indraśatroḥ kṛtvā ca pādaṃ śirasi prasahya|
triśūlam ādāya bibheda pṛṣṭhe vyayojayaccāsubhirāśu daityam|| 68.23||
kuliśakaṭhinaśṛṅgaṃ nīlajīmūtakalpaṃ mahiṣam atha nihatya prauḍhadarpaṃ tadānīm|
vividhakusumavṛṣṭyā sarvataḥ kīryamāṇā dharaṇidharam agacchat kauśikī sannivāsam|| 68.24||
iti skandapurāṇe
mahiṣāsuravadho nāmāṣṭaṣaṣṭitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 68.68||

ūnasaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan sarvalokajña pitāmahasamudyate|
tapaḥ kṛtvā tadā devī puṣkalaṃ himavatsutā|| 69.1||
varaṃ yathepsitaṃ labdhvā brahmaṇo gauravarṇatām|
kim anyadakarodvipra tapaso 'ante mahāmune|| 69.2||
somanandī ca śārdūlaḥ kim avāpa varaṃ śubham|
etanme pṛcchato brūhi bhaktāya praṇatāya ca|| 69.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
namaskṛtya mahādevaṃ paramaṃ brahma śāśvatam|
yaṃ paṭhanti sadā sāṃkhyāḥ puruṣaṃ paṃcaviṃsakam|| 69.4||
yoginaścaiva ṣaḍviṃśaṃ brahmādyāśca divaukasaḥ|
praṇamya parayā bhaktyā śirasā taṃ trilocanam|| 69.5||
gauryā samāgamo vyāsa śaṅkarasya yathābhavat|
tat pravakṣyāmi te sarvaṃ śṛṇu yogavidāṃ vara|| 69.6||
tasmin himavataḥ śṛṅge tapaḥ kṛtvā suduṣkaram|
gaurāṅgī sā tadā bhūtvā śuddhahemasamaprabhā|| 69.7||
darśane śaṅkarasyātha śarvāṇī matim ādadhe|
mandaraṃ girim āgamya sahitā somanandinā|| 69.8||
apaśyadbhavane bhartuḥ svāramūle samāsthitam|
nandinaṃ gaṇapaṃ devī dīptapaṭṭiśadhāriṇam|| 69.9||
tato nandīśvaraṃ dṛṣṭvā bhaktaṃ premṇā girīndrajā|
ehi vatsa cirāddṛṣṭastvam ityuktavatī tadā|| 69.10||
nandī saṃprekṣya tāṃ cāpi gaurāṅgīṃ hemasaprabhām|
harṣeṇa mahatā yuktaḥ pādayorapatadbhṛśam|| 69.11||
praṇamya sa tadā dhīmānastuvat parvatātmajām|
namaḥ siddhyai mahādevyai rataye gataye namaḥ|| 69.12||
tvaṃ kriyā kāraṇaṃ tvaṃ ca prakṛtirmuktireva ca|
āntirdyutistathā tuṣṭiḥ śāntiḥ svastyayanaṃ param|| 69.13||
dakṣiṇā niyatirmṛtyuḥ sandhyā vidyudahaḥ kṣapā|
pṛthivī kauśikī śrīśca śarvāṇī śarvavallabhā|| 69.14||
gaṇamātā ditiścaiva pavitrā vindhyavāsinī|
kṛṣṇā kātyāyanī gaurī bhūtamātā tatheśvarī|| 69.15||
bhava devi prasannā me bhaktasya praṇatasya ca|
atha devī tadā dṛṣṭvā nandinaṃ pādayornatam|| 69.16||
provāca varadāsmīti sa ca vavre varaṃ śubham|
prasannāṃ nityam eva tvām icchāmi varam uttamam|| 69.17||
evam astviti sā procya praviveśāyatekṣaṇā|
agrato 'asyā yayau nandī somanandī ca pṛṣṭhataḥ|| 69.18||
candralekhobhayormadhye grahayoriva sā babhau|
dūrādeva samālokya devadevo mudānvitaḥ|| 69.19||
ājagāma mahātejāḥ saṃbhramotphullalocanaḥ|
papāta pādayordevī devadevasya dhīmataḥ|| 69.20||
atha devastadāyātāṃ devīṃ girivarātmajām|
samuvāca suraśreṣṭhaḥ samālokya muhurmuhuḥ|| 69.21||
diṣṭyāsi prītavadanā diṣṭyā ca saphalaṃ tapaḥ|
diṣṭyā cedaṃ varaṃ varṇaṃ gauraṃ kanakasaprabham|| 69.22||
priyaṃ naḥ sarvathā devi paramaṃ yat tvam āgatā|
pratijñāṃ pūrayitveha śārdūlo 'ayaṃ kutaśca te|| 69.23||
evam uktā tadā devī bhartrā praṇayapeśalam|
kathayāmāsa devāya sarvaṃ caritam ātmanaḥ|| 69.24||
devyuvāca|
prāgahaṃ yat tvayā deva kṛṣṇavarṇeti bhāṣitā|
tadā manyuparītāṅgī gauravarṇasamīpsayā|| 69.25||
himavacchikharaṃ gatvā tapo 'ahaṃ mahadāsthitā|
cintayantī sadaiva tvām ekapādena saṃsthitā|| 69.26||
yasminneva dine tatra tapo 'ahaṃ samupāśritā|
tasminnevaiṣa śārdūlaḥ somanandī mamāgrataḥ|| 69.27||
vyatiṣṭhata mahādeva bhaktyā paramayā yutaḥ|
divyaṃ varṣasahasraṃ tat tapoyuktāham āsthitā|| 69.28||
tāvantaṃ kālam eṣo 'api mamātiṣṭhat samīpataḥ|
stabdhalāṅgūlanetrāsyo nirāhāro vilokayan|| 69.29||
āgatastapasaścānte brahmā mama varapradaḥ|
tam ahaṃ pūrvam asyārthe varaṃ saṃprārthayaṃ vibho|| 69.30||
tenāyam amaro deva jarāśokavivarjitaḥ|
mamaivānucaraḥ pārśve kṛto yogī ca śaṅkara|
varṇaṃ cedam adānmahyaṃ tavādeśāt pitāmahaḥ|| 69.31||
devadeva uvāca|
parituṣṭo 'asmi te devi varaṃ vṛṇu yathepsitam|
mṛgendro 'ayaṃ gaṇaśreṣṭhaḥ somanandī mahābalaḥ|| 69.32||
yādṛśo mama nandīśastādṛśaste bhaviṣyati|
yadanyadbrūhi tat sarvaṃ kariṣyāmi tava priye|| 69.33||
devyuvāca|
yasmin deśe mahādeva tapaścaritam uttamam|
taṃ bhūyo 'api tvayā sārdhaṃ draṣṭum icchāmi śaṅkara|| 69.34||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktaḥ sa pārvatyā provāca parameśvaraḥ|
rocate cārusarvāṅgi gantuṃ tatra mamāvyaye|| 69.35||
ramyaṃ taddhimavacchṛṅgaṃ taptaṃ yatra tapastvayā|
nandinaṃ sa tadāhūya gaṇapāṃśca sahasraśaḥ|| 69.36||
jagāma sahito devyā himavantaṃ mahāgirim|
devairvidyādharaiḥ siddhairgandharvairmunisattamaiḥ|| 69.37||
vandyamāno 'asakṛddevaḥ stūyamānaśca sarvaśaḥ|
nandinaḥ pṛṣṭham ārūḍhaḥ prakrīḍitagaṇeśvaraḥ|| 69.38||
himavadgirim āgamya taṃ pradeśam upāgamat|
sa taṃ śikharam āsādya ramyadhātuvibhūṣitam|| 69.39||
tutoṣa paramaprīto reme ca sagaṇeśvaraḥ|
āgataṃ tam atho dṛṣṭvā mūrimānacalastadā|
upatasthe mahādevaṃ praṇipatya kṛtāñjaliḥ|| 69.40||
kṛtvā tadarghakuṇḍaṃ tu tasmiñchikharasattame|
varadānena śailendram anvagṛhṇāt pinākadhṛk|| 69.41||
amaro jarayā tyaktaḥ sarvaduḥkhavivarjitaḥ|
abhedyaścaiva vajreṇa matprasādādbhaviṣyasi|| 69.42||
puṇyastvam acalaśreṣṭha bhavitā pāpamocanaḥ|
gaurīśikhara ityeva loke khyātiṃ gamiṣyasi|| 69.43||
dūrādeva nagaśreṣṭha dṛṣṭvā tvām ucchritaṃ janāḥ|
sarvapāpairvimokṣyante yāssyanti ca parāṃ gatim|| 69.44||
trirātram uṣito yastvām abhiruhya śucivrataḥ|
dṛṣṭvā gaurīm athābhyarcya brāhaṇaṃ tarpayiṣyati|| 69.45||
nārī vātha naro vāpi lokaṃ gauryāḥ sa yāsyati|
yaśceha tyakṣyate prāṇān niyamena samāhitaḥ|| 69.46||
sa gāṇapatyaṃ samprāpya mayā sārdhaṃ cariṣyati|
gauryāścātraiva sānnidhyaṃ sarvadā te bhaviṣyati|| 69.47||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ityuktvā taṃ nagaśreṣṭhaṃ devadevastrilocanaḥ|
pārvatyā sahitastatra paricakrāma sarvataḥ|| 69.48||
athāpaśyacchilāṃ vyāsa sauvarṇāṃ maṇibhūṣitām|
kathayāmāsa tāṃ devyai śilāṃ paśyeti a prabhuḥ|| 69.49||
tam āha devī deveśam iha taptaṃ mayā tapaḥ|
priyam evaṃ mama sthānaṃ somanandina eva ca|| 69.50||
atha tām anujagrāha śilāṃ prītyā bhavastadā|
śucirasyāṃ nirāhāraṃ trirātraṃ yaḥ kariṣyati|| 69.51||
bhavet taptaṃ tapastena lokaṃ ca tava yāsyati|
ekapādena yo martyastiṣṭhedekam ahaḥ śuciḥ|| 69.52||
tapanābhimukho bhūtvā tvadbhaktastvatparāyaṇaḥ|
so 'api yāsyati te lokaṃ gaṇapaśca bhaviṣyati|| 69.53||
prāṇān parityajedyaśca śilāyām iha dustyajān|
so 'api taptatapā bhūtvā brahmalokaṃ gamiṣyati|| 69.54||
imaṃ ca parvatoddeśam āspadaṃ somanandinaḥ|
yo 'abhigacchedahorātraṃ so 'api nandisamo bhavet|| 69.55||
athāpṛcchat punardevaḥ pārvatīṃ vicaran prabhuḥ|
katham etāni kuṇḍāni babhūvuriha śailaje|| 69.56||
evaṃ pṛṣṭā punardevī vākyam etajjagāda ha|
yadāham āgatā deva tapastaptum iha prabho|| 69.57||
stanayoḥ prasrute dhāre mahatyau me tadāsakṛt|
ete tābhyāṃ kṛte kuṇḍe sitatoye mahāplave|| 69.58||
tapastaptum alaṅkārānahaṃ tyaktavatī yadā|
tadā tebhyaḥ srutā deva jaladhārāpataddrutam|| 69.59||
tayā cedam apāṃ kuṇḍaṃ dvitīyaṃ me kṛtaṃ śubham|
brahmaṇaśca yadā labdhaṃ gauravarṇatvam uttamam|| 69.60||
śarīrānme tadā deva kṛṣṇā kośī viniṣkramat|
tasyāṃ kośyāṃ samutpannam etat kuṇḍaṃ tṛtīyakam|| 69.61||
asmin pradeśe deveśa tvām abhyarcya yathāvidhi|
havirbhirmantrayuktābhiragnikāryaṃ kṛtaṃ mayā|| 69.62||
imāni pādapasthāni valkalāni samāsate|
idaṃ kṛṣṇājinaṃ śubhraṃ sthāpitaṃ tat purā mayā|| 69.63||
atha śrutvā mahādevaḥ pārvatyā vacanaṃ prabhuḥ|
pratyuvāca tadā devīṃ prītyā paramayā yutaḥ|| 69.64||
stanatoyena yat pūrṇe tava kuṇḍe śaśiprabhe|
stanakuṇḍeti tenaite yāsyete khyātim uttamām|| 69.65||
upavāsī nato yo 'atra snātvābhyarcya ca devatāḥ|
tarpayitvā pitR̥n sarvān brāhmaṇān bhojayiṣyati|| 69.66||
tadbhavedakṣayaṃ tasya gaṇaścaiva bhaviṣyati|
alaṃkārāt srutā dhārā yeyaṃ tava varānane|| 69.67||
eṣālaṃkāradhāreti nāmnā khyātiṃ gamiṣyati|
asyāṃ snātvā naro yastu pitR̥n saṃtarpayiṣyati|| 69.68||
akṣayaṃ tadbhavecchrāddham aśvamedhaṃ ca vindati|
nīlatoyam idaṃ yat te mahat kuṇḍaṃ śubhodakam|| 69.69||
nīlakuṇḍam iti khyātim etat sarvatra yāsyati|
yo 'asmin niyamavān snātva tarpayet pitṛdevatāḥ|| 69.70||
tasyākṣayaṃ bhavet sarvaṃ pāpebhyaḥ sa pramucyate|
mṛtaśca sa naro devi yatra tatra yathā tathā|| 69.71||
kauśikyā vindhyavāsinyā mahāgaṇapatirbhavet|
agnikāryam iha snātvā yaḥ kuryādbrāhmaṇaḥ śuciḥ|| 69.72||
agnihotraṃ hutaṃ tena bhavet svādaśavārṣikam|
evam uktvā mahādevaḥ protthāya munisattama|| 69.73||
gṛhītvā pādapasthāni valkalāni tadā prabhuḥ|
nadī bhaveti samprocya cikṣepa prahasanniva|| 69.74||
tānyabhūvaṃstadā vyāsa nadī svacchajalā śubhā|
taṭajairvividhairvṛkṣairhaṃsacakrāhvaśobhitā|| 69.75||
tām uvāca suraśreṣṭhaḥ puṇyatoyāṃ mahānadīm|
cīrebhyo nissṛtā yasmāt tvam atra saritāṃ varā|| 69.76||
loke puṇyatamā tasmānniścīreti bhaviṣyasi|
tvayi snātvā naraḥ kṣipraṃ sarvapāpairvimucyate|| 69.77||
pitR̥n santarpayedyastu śrāddhaṃ tasyākṣayaṃ bhavet|
kapilāṃ cātra yo dadyādbrāhmaṇāya samāhitaḥ|| 69.78||
gosahasraphalaṃ tasya bhaviṣyati varānane|
agram āruhya yasmāt tvam atra taptavatī tapaḥ|| 69.79||
agrāraṇyam iti khyātim etadyāsyati sarvataḥ|
mahāphalaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ sarvasiddhipradaṃ śubham|| 69.80||
pañcayojanasaṃsthānaṃ gaurīśikharam uttamam|
ihopoṣya śuciḥ snātvā bhaktyā paramayā yutaḥ|| 69.81||
dehabhedaṃ samāsādya vimānastho virājate|
kṛṣṇājinaṃ mahāpuṇyaṃ sarvapāpaharaṃ tava|| 69.82||
idaṃ draṣyati yo vipraḥ svargastasya na durlabhaḥ|
yat phalaṃ naimiśāraṇye puṣkareṣu ca yat phalam|| 69.83||
tadeva labhate devi dṛṣṭvā kṛṣṇājinaṃ dvijaḥ|
vatsyāmi caiva satataṃ tvayā sārdham iha priye|| 69.84||
āvām iha sthitau devi yo 'arcayiṣyati mānavaḥ|
āvayorgaṇapo bhūtvā jagat sarvaṃ cariṣyati|| 69.85||
evaṃ nagendraṃ sa tadānugṛhya munīndra sārdhaṃ girirājaputryā|
devaiḥ sasiddhairanugamyamānaḥ śarvaḥ punarmandaram ājagām|| 69.86||
iti skandapurāṇe devīsamāgame
kośīśilāstanakuṇḍājinagaurīśikharavarapradānaṃ nāma
ūnasaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 69.69||

saptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
sa gatvā mandaraṃ bhūyo giriputryā saha prabhuḥ|
yaccakāra mahādevastanme brūhi mahāmune|| 70.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
mandaraṃ girim āgatya pārvatyā sahito haraḥ|
reme hiraṇmaye divye sarvaratnavibhūṣite|| 70.2||
cārusopānasaṃkīrṇe citrapaṭṭaśilātale|
tasmin puravare śreṣṭhe manasā nirmite tadā|| 70.3||
gaṇeśvarairmahāyogairnandīśvarapurogamaiḥ|
siddhairmunivaraiścaiva sevyamāno jagatpatiḥ|| 70.4||
uvāsa sahito devyā vandyamānastathaiva ca|
tasyaivaṃ dīvyato vyāsa devadevasya dhīmataḥ|| 70.5||
sahasrākṣaḥ śaśāṅkaśca vāyuścaiva tadā gatāḥ|
samāgamya puradvāraṃ dṛṣṭvā te nandinaṃ sthitam|| 70.6||
ūcuḥ prāñjalayo bhūtvā śaṅkaraṃ saṃdidṛkṣavaḥ|
yathā paśyāma deveśaṃ nandiṃstat kartum arhasi|| 70.7||
atha nandī samāgatya dvāramūle samāsthitaḥ|
śambhornivedayāmāsa trīn devāṃstu samāgatān|| 70.8||
viśantviti samājñapte devadevena nandini|
viviśuste trayo devāḥ śaṅkarasyāntikaṃ tadā|| 70.9||
praṇamya sahitāstasthuḥ paśyanto varadaṃ vibhum|
atha tān prāha lokeśaḥ śirobhiḥ praṇatān sthitān|| 70.10||
kā vaḥ kartavyatā devāḥ kimarthaṃ yūyam āgatāḥ|
brūta dāsyāmi tat sarvaṃ yadyanmṛgayathāmarāḥ|| 70.11||
atha devaḥ sahasrākṣo vacaḥ provāca śaṅkaram|
hiraṇyakaśipuṃ hantum asurendraṃ mahābalam|| 70.12||
yaccakāra vapurviṣṇurnārasiṃhaṃ bhayānakam|
taṃ hatvāpi sa daityendraṃ viṣṇuḥ parabalārdanaḥ|| 70.13||
tadrūpaṃ naiva santyajya svaṃ veṣam akarodvibho|
tena rūpeṇa deveśa krūreṇāpi hitepsunā|| 70.14||
na vayaṃ nirvṛtā bhūtvā trāsāt tiṣṭhāma śaṅkara|
sa yathā siṃharūpaṃ tat parityajati mādhavaḥ|| 70.15||
prasādaṃ nastathā kartum arhasi tvaṃ surottama|
atha provāca taṃ śakraṃ devadevaḥ pinākadhṛk|| 70.16||
siṃharūpaṃ yathā śakra viṣṇustyakṣyati bhīṣaṇam|
kariṣyāmi tathā śakra vyetu te mānaso jvaraḥ|| 70.17||
atha vāyustadā devaṃ vyajñāpayata śaṃkaram|
aśarīro yathā na syāṃ tathā me kartum arhasi|| 70.18||
śrutvā pavanavijñaptiṃ devastasmai trilocanaḥ|
śarīraṃ sumahat prādādyenāsau mūrtimānabhūt|| 70.19||
vijñāpitaṃ śaśāṅkena tato vyāsa mahātmanā|
dakṣeṇāhaṃ purā śapto yakṣmadeho bhaviṣyasi|| 70.20||
sa yathā yakṣmahīnaḥ syāṃ prasādam me tathā kuru|
vijñaptiṃ śaśinaḥ śrutvā devastasmai vacaḥ prabhuḥ|| 70.21||
idaṃ prāha mahātejāḥ śaśine praṇatāya tu|
tapaḥ kṛtvā prabhāse tvaṃ yakṣmahīno bhaviṣyasi|| 70.22||
iti labdhvā varaṃ sarve trayo 'api surasattamāḥ|
vāyusomasahasrākṣāḥ svāni veśmāni bhejire|| 70.23||
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan sa kathaṃ tena narasiṃhena sūditaḥ|
hiraṇyakaśipurdaityaḥ kiṃprabhāvaśca so 'abhavat|
kiṃ vīryaṃ kiṃ tapaścāsya śaṃsaitat pṛcchato mama|| 70.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ditirnāmābhavat patnī kaśyapasya prajāpateḥ|
dakṣasya duhitā vyāsa sā jajñe tanayadvayam|| 70.25||
hiraṇyakaśipuṃ jyeṣṭhaṃ hiraṇyākṣaṃ kanīyasam|
abhiṣiktaḥ sa daityānāṃ rājābhūdbrahmaṇā purā|| 70.26||
dānavānām athendratve vipracittirmahābalaḥ|
sahasrākṣaśca devānām etadindratrayaṃ babhau|| 70.27||
atha teṣāṃ tadā vyāsa trailokyaṃ saṃpraśāsatām|
hiraṇyakaśipurdaityaḥ śakrarājyajihīrṣayā|| 70.28||
trailokyam ātmasāt kartuṃ matiṃ tapasi sandadhe|
sa gatvā dakṣiṇām āśāṃ śrīparvatasamāsthitaḥ|| 70.29||
tapastīvraṃ mahat tepe daityarājo mahābalaḥ|
svaraktena juhāvāgnau saṃmiśrāḥ samidhaścarūn|| 70.30||
ūrdhvabāhurnirālambo divā sūryārpitekṣaṇaḥ|
ekapādo 'animeṣaśca so 'atiṣṭhat kṛtaniścayaḥ|| 70.31||
dve sahasre tadābdānāṃ divyānāṃ sthitavān balī|
mahatā tapasā tasya trailokyaṃ sampracukṣubhe|| 70.32||
athābhyetya suraśreṣṭho brahmā kamalavāhanaḥ|
iṣṭaṃ vṛṇu varaṃ rājanniti provāca sādaram|| 70.33||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā daityarājastu brahmāṇaṃ varadaṃ prabhum|
varaṃ prārthitavān vyāsa śṛṇu yādṛśam īpsitam|| 70.34||
bhagavan yadi tuṣṭo 'asi vara eṣo 'astu me vibho|
amaraḥ syām avadhyaśca jarāhīno mahābalaḥ|| 70.35||
na śatreṇa na cāstreṇa na rātrau na divā tathā|
naivārdreṇa na śuṣkeṇa na puṃsā na ca yoṣitā|| 70.36||
abravīt so 'antaraṃ brahmā sa cainaṃ samabhāṣata|
ataśca yo 'anyathā mṛtyurbhaviṣyati sa me prabho|| 70.37||
evam astviti taṃ procya brahmā suravarottamaḥ|
jagāmātmapuraṃ kṣipraṃ śāntaḥ prītaḥ pitāmahaḥ|| 70.38||
so 'api sarvāsuraśreṣṭho hiraṇyakaśipustadā|
jitvā śakraṃ svayaṃ rājyaṃ cakāra ditinandanaḥ|| 70.39||
trailokyam ātmasātkṛtvā jitvā sarvān divaukasaḥ|
ātmanaivābhavacchakraḥ svayaṃ vāyuḥ svayaṃ yamaḥ|
dhaneśo varuṇo vahniḥ sarva evābhavat svayam|| 70.40||
praṇamadhvaṃ yajadhvaṃ māṃ brahmāhaṃ sapurandaraḥ|
iti prāha ṛṣīn sarvān siddhān viprāṃśca so 'asuraḥ|| 70.41||
vyāsa uvāca|
śrīparvata iti prokto yastvayā munisattama|
kathaṃ śrīparvato 'asau vai kiṃ puṇyaṃ tatra kiṃ phalam|| 70.42||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
hanta te kathayiṣyāmi yanmāṃ pṛcchasi suvrata|
hiraṇyakaśipurdaityo yatra tepe mahat tapaḥ|| 70.43||
girau tasmin mahāpuṇye devadevo vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
umayā sahito devyā reme nityaṃ mahādyutiḥ|| 70.44||
tiṣṭhatastatra devasya devī girivarātmajā|
tapaḥsiddhān mahāyogāñjvalanādityavarcasaḥ|| 70.45||
kṛtvā pradakṣiṇāṃ śambhoḥ sapraṇāmaṃ mahāmune|
gacchatastān muhurdṛṣṭvā papraccha bhuvaneśvaram|| 70.46||
ka ete deva saṃsiddhā yogīśāstvāṃ praṇemire|
tato devaḥ prahasyainām uvāca parameśvaraḥ|| 70.47||
yogasiddhā mahātmāno yoge pāśupate sthitāḥ|
ya ihārādhya māṃ devi jahuḥ prāṇān narottamāḥ|| 70.48||
ta ete siddhadehārthāḥ svacchandagaticāriṇaḥ|
mokṣasiddheḥ parāṃ niṣṭhāṃ gantāraḥ paramaṃ padam|| 70.49||
atha saṃcintya suciraṃ vismayāyatalocanā|
devaṃ provāca śarvāṇī vacaḥ paramapūjitam|| 70.50||
yathāham api deveśa prāpnuyāṃ siddhim īdṛśīm|
kariṣyāmi tathā yatnam eṣā cāsmi gatā vibho|| 70.51||
tataḥ kṛtvā śriyo rūpaṃ devī paramaśobhanā|
mahat tatra tapastepe sahasraṃ parivatsarān|| 70.52||
devaścāsyā varaṃ prādāt taiḥ samānaṃ mahādyutiḥ|
kṛtsnasyādhyātmatantrasya mayā proktasya bhāmini|| 70.53||
mahāyogeśvarī siddhā parārthajñā bhaviṣyasi|
ayaṃ ca parvataḥ śrīmān nāmnā tava bhaviṣyasi|| 70.54|
śrīparvata iti khyātaścitrarūpavibhūṣitaḥ|
samantādyojanaśataṃ mahāpuṇyo bhaviṣyasi|| 70.55||
ihāgamya ca yo devi tvāṃ māṃ ca girinandane|
śuciḥ snātvārcayenmartyaḥ sa lokaṃ mama yāsyati|| 70.56||
yastviha tyakṣyate prāṇāñchrīgirāvacalottame|
trinetraḥ kāmago bhūtvā gāṇapatyam avāpnuyāt|| 70.57||
ihāgatya ca ye śailaṃ kariṣyanti pradakṣiṇam|
śarvāyatanasaṃyuktaṃ bhaviṣyanti ca te gaṇāḥ|| 70.58||
atiśayaramaṇīye siddhasaṃghairupete surabhikusumacitre śrīgirau ye pumāṃsaḥ|
vyapagatamaladoṣā māṃ prapaśyanti śuddhā viyati vihagayuktaiste vimānaiḥ prayānti|| 70.59||
iti skandapurāṇe
śrīgirivarapradānaṃ nāma
saptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 70.70||

ekasaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śāsatastasya daityasya hiraṇyakaśipostadā|
agāt kālo mahān vyāsa trailokyaṃ sacarācaram|| 71.1||
darpeṇa mahatāviṣṭaḥ śrīmadodvṛttacetanaḥ|
avamene surān sarvān na ca dharmam avaikṣata|| 71.2||
sa devān sahitān sarvāñchakrādyān krodhamūrchitaḥ|
cālitānapi rājye sve kṛcchram āpādayadbhṛśam|| 71.3||
santāpyamānāste sarve brahmāṇaṃ śaraṇaṃ yayuḥ|
bhagavan bhūtabhavyeśa pitāmaha mahādyute|| 71.4||
hiraṇyakaśipurdaityastvatto labdhavaro 'anagha|
trailokyaṃ kṛtsnam ākramya rājyaṃ no hṛtavān divaḥ|| 71.5||
aniśaṃ cāvamānan naḥ prayuṅkte vairayātanam|
tena vidrāvitāḥ sarve śaraṇaṃ vayam āgatāḥ|| 71.6||
prasādaṃ kuru deveśa sa na syānno yathā ripuḥ|
tyaktadharmā jagacchatrurhiraṇyakaśipurbalī|| 71.7||
evaṃ proktastadā devairdevaḥ kamalavāhanaḥ|
provācedaṃ mahāprajña devānāṃ pritakṛdvacaḥ|| 71.8||
kṣīṇaṃ taddaityarājasya tapastasya durātmanaḥ|
kṛcchraṃ gamitavān yo vo rājyaṃ ca hṛtavān ripuḥ|| 71.9||
tenāhaṃ prārthitaḥ pūrvaṃ sarvāvadhyatvam uttamam|
antaraṃ bhāṣitaścāsau mayā saṃjñāvimohitaḥ|| 71.10||
yadaivāntaram āhātha daityarājo vicetanaḥ|
tadaiva manasā toṣam aham āgāṃ mahābalāḥ|| 71.11||
te yūyam adya gacchadhvaṃ viṣṇorbhavanam uttamam|
taṃ brūta sahitāḥ sarve tasya nāśārtham acyutam|| 71.12||
narasiṃhavapuḥ kṛtvā sakṛdāhatya haṃsyati|
hiraṇyakaśipuṃ daityaṃ tato nivṛtim eṣyatha|| 71.13||
evam astviti te sarve praṇipatya pitāmaham|
ājagmuḥ sahitā devā viṣṇorbhavanam ādṛtāḥ|| 71.14||
atha dṛṣṭvā mahātejā viṣṇurdevānupasthitān|
uvāca ślakṣṇayā vācā vacaścoktimanoharam|| 71.15||
svāgataṃ bhavatām astu kimarthaṃ yūyam āgatāḥ|
pūjyā bhavantaḥ sarve me suhṛdo 'atigarīyasaḥ|| 71.16||
yadvo manogataṃ kiṃcinmayā kāryaṃ divaukasaḥ|
kṣipraṃ tadbrūta saṃkṣiptaṃ kartāham avicāritam|| 71.17||
viṣṇunaivaṃ tadā proktā devāḥ śakrapurogamāḥ|
ūcuḥ prahṛṣṭavadanāḥ saṃstuvanto janārdanam|| 71.18||
hiraṇyakaśipordeva daityarājo mahābalāt|
bhayaṃ naḥ sumahajjātaṃ rājyaṃ cāpahṛtaṃ divaḥ|| 71.19||
avamānaḥ prayuktaśca tenāsmabhyaṃ surottama|
bhunakti sa jagat kṛtsnaṃ brahmavit kaśyapātmajaḥ|| 71.20||
sa yathā vadhyate daityastvayā sarvārisūdana|
tathā kuru hṛṣīkeśa varo 'ayaṃ naḥ pradīyatām|| 71.21||
tato viṣṇuściraṃ dhyātvā vadhopāyaṃ pracintya ca|
prāha devān suraśreṣṭho vacasāpyāyayanniva|| 71.22||
evam astu suraśreṣṭhaḥ sarvaṃ kartāsmi vo vacaḥ|
mahābalaḥ sa daityendro yato yuṣmān vadāmyaham|| 71.23||
āviśantu bhavanto 'api śarīraṃ mama suvratāḥ|
sarvadevamayo bhūtvā dṛptaṃ haṃsyāmi vo ripum|| 71.24||
tato devāstadā sarve viviśurvaiṣṇavīṃ tanum|
sa cāpi balavān bhūtvā rūpaṃ kṛtvā bhayānakam|| 71.25||
nārasiṃhaṃ mahātejā nakhadaṃṣṭrāvibhūṣaṇam|
jagāma vilasadviṣṇurhiraṇyakaśipoḥ puram|| 71.26||
udyānaṃ sa bahistasya sarvartukusumairvṛtam|
nṛsiṃho daityasiṃhasya dṛsṭvā tasthau suvismitaḥ|| 71.27||
campakāśokajātībhiḥ kadambairbakulairapi|
tathā surabhipuṣpaiśca samantādupaśobhitam|| 71.28||
sarobhiḥ padmasaṃcchannairhaṃsacakrāhvaśobhitaiḥ|
vṛkṣaiḥ kāmaphalaiścaiva vaibhrājasadṛśaṃ vanam|| 71.29||
tadbabhañja nṛsiṃhastu khelagāmī mahotkaṭaḥ|
sarāṃsi kṣobhayāmāsa karīva sa madolvaṇaḥ|| 71.30||
sa reje vanamadhyasthaḥ parisarpannitastataḥ|
meroracalarājasya sthitaṃ śṛṅgam ivocchritam|| 71.31||
athābhyetya nṛsiṃhaṃ taṃ vanapālā ruṣānvitāḥ|
balino vārayāmāsustāṃścaivābhyahanadbalī|| 71.32||
hataśeṣāstatastatra pravilīnāstu ye 'asurāḥ|
te gatvā kathayāmāsurhiraṇyakaśipostadā|| 71.33||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā daityarājo mahābalaḥ|
prahlādaṃ cānuhlādaṃ ca namuciṃ bāṣkaliṃ balim|| 71.34||
vipracittipradhānāṃśca sarvān āhūya dānavān|
provāca tvaritaṃ gatvā baddhvā siṃhaṃ mamāntikam|| 71.35||
samānayata daityendrā na hantavyaḥ kathaṃcana|
krīḍaṇaṃ siṃhapoto 'asau devyā mama bhaviṣyati|| 71.36||
iti śrutvāsurāḥ sarve vipracittipurogamāḥ|
udyānaṃ sahitā gatvā nṛsiṃhaṃ dadṛśuḥ sthitam|| 71.37||
dūrasthāścikṣipuḥ pāśāṃstān sa ciccheda mādhavaḥ|
atha vidrāvayāmāsa dānavān keśarī bhṛśam|| 71.38||
tato hatasahāyāste daityā vimanaso yayuḥ|
pārśvaṃ dānavarājasya sarvaṃ cākathayaṃstadā|| 71.39||
atha kruddhaḥ svayaṃ rājā hiraṇyakaśipurbalī|
ratham āsthāya sannaddhā nṛsiṃhaṃ prādravadruṣā|| 71.40||
sa rathaḥ siṃharājena sāyudhaḥ parvatopamaḥ|
sambhrāmya pātitastūrṇaṃ cūrṇam āgānmahītale|| 71.41||
tato bhagnaratho daityaḥ krodhāt saṃraktalocanaḥ|
vṛkṣam utpāṭya vegena nṛsiṃhāya vyasarjayat|| 71.42||
athāsau patito gātre siṃharājasya pādapaḥ|
mṛtkhaṇḍa iva pāṣāṇe kṣiptaścūrṇaṃ jagāma ha|| 71.43||
gṛhītvā sa tadā siṃho hiraṇyakaśipuṃ sakṛt|
talenāhatya taṃ prāṇairvyayojayata satvaram|| 71.44||
siṃhanādaṃ mahat kṛtvā nakhairvajramayairvibhuḥ|
uro bibheda daityasya mahāśailopamaṃ hariḥ|| 71.45||
haste tasmin mahādaitye viṣṇunā śaktinandana|
dānavā na hatā ye tu viviśuste rasātalam|| 71.46||
divo rājyaṃ punaḥ śakro lebhe niṣkaṇṭakaṃ mahat|
divaukasaśca sarve te svāni rājyāni bhejire|| 71.47||
athāgatya tato devaḥ śūlapāṇirvṛṣadhvajaḥ|
surairvijñāpito vyāsa yat te kathitavānaham|| 71.48||
viṣṇostyājayituṃ rūpaṃ saiṃham adbhutakarmaṇaḥ|
śarabhaḥ sa tadā bhūtvā himavacchikharopamaḥ|| 71.49||
caturbhiḥ pṛṣṭhajaiḥ pādaistīkṣṇadaṃṣṭro mahābalaḥ|
narasiṃhasamīpaṃ tu gatvāgarjat samāhitaḥ|| 71.50||
atha siṃhastadā dṛṣṭvā śarabhaṃ samupasthitam|
krodhena mahatāviṣṭastalenainam atāḍayat|| 71.51||
sa hatastena siṃhena śarabho naiva cukṣubhe|
tataḥ śarabham āhatya vajradehaṃ mahābalam|| 71.52||
ātmanaivāgamat kṛcchraṃ sparśāt tasya mahātmanaḥ|
tato viṣṇuściraṃ dhyātvā jñātvā śaṃkaram āgatam|| 71.53||
praṇamya śirasā taṃ vai stotum evaṃ pracakrame|
namaḥ śarvāya rudrāya senānye śarmadāya ca|| 71.54||
namaḥ paramadevāya brahmaṇe paramāya ca|
kālāya yamarūpāya kāladaṇḍāya vai namaḥ|| 71.55||
namaḥ kālāntakartre ca kālekālaharāya ca|
namaḥ pinākahastāya raudrabāṇadharāya ca|| 71.56||
caṇḍāya vāmadevāya sarvayogeśvarāya ca|
namo vidyādhipataye brahmaṇaḥ pataye namaḥ|| 71.57||
namo 'asuravaraghnāya kālacakrāya te namaḥ|
saṃvarttakāgnicakrāya pralayāntakarāya ca|| 71.58||
naranārāyaṇeśāya naranārāyaṇātmane|
mamaiva varadātre ca sarvakāmapradāya ca|| 71.59||
śarabhāya surūpāya vyāghracarmasuvāsase|
nandīśvaragaṇeśāya gaṇānāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 71.60||
indriyāṇām atheśāya manasaspataye namaḥ|
namaḥ pradhānapataye surāṇāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 71.61||
namo 'astu bhāvapataye tattvānāṃ pataye namaḥ|
carācarāṇāṃ pataye bhūtānāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 71.62||
trailokyapataye caiva lokānāṃ pataye namaḥ|
yogadāya mano mahyaṃ tathaivaiśvaryadāya ca|| 71.63||
avadhyatvapradātre ca tathaivājapyadāya ca|
bhagavaṃstvatpratiṣṭho 'asmi tvanniṣṭhastvatparāyaṇaḥ|
śaraṇaṃ tvāṃ prapanno 'ahaṃ prasīda mama sarvadā|| 71.64||
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyānnityaṃ śuciḥ prayatamānasaḥ|
sa rudralokam āsādya devasya gaṇapo bhavet|| 71.65||
dhanyaṃ yaśasyam āyuṣyaṃ svargyaṃ pāpapraṇāśanam|
śrāvaṇaṃ śravaṇaṃ cāsya tathānusmaraṇaṃ sadā|| 71.66||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evaṃ stūyamānastu viṣṇunā bhuvaneśvaraḥ|
hṛṣīkeśam uvācedaṃ vacaḥ paramapūjitam|| 71.67||
tubhyaṃ viṣṇo mayā dattaḥ puṇyo hyeṣa varaḥ śubhaḥ|
ayonau sajjamānasya svayonau pratipādanam|| 71.68||
sa tvaṃ viṣṇurmahātejā matto labdhavaraḥ sadā|
velāyāṃ tvāṃ samudrastu tiryagyonim asūta yas (?)|| 71.69||
kṛtaṃ kāryaṃ tvayā sarvaṃ hiraṇyakaśipurhataḥ|
ehi gaccha śubhāṃ yonim ātmanaḥ paramādbhutām|| 71.70||
tatastam ākramat pādaiḥ siṃhaṃ śarabhasattamaḥ|
ayojayacca dehena puno divyena keśavam|| 71.71||
viṣṇave 'atha varaṃ dattvā daityaghnaṃ sa vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
prakṛtistho bhavetyuktvā tatraivāntaradhīyata|| 71.72||
dattvā tasmai varam anupamaṃ viṣṇave lokadhātā daityaghnatvaṃ surapuravadhūlocanaiḥ pīyamānaḥ|
nīlāmbhodadyutinibham uraḥ prodvahacchūlapāṇirdhāma svīyaṃ paramamunibhirvandyamāno jagāma|| 71.73||
iti skandapurāṇe hiraṇyakaśipūpakhyāne
śarabhakṛtanarasiṃhoddhārākhyānaṃ nāma
ekasaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 71.71||

dvisaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan sarvayogajña śrutam ākhyānam uttamam|
parataḥ śrotum icchāmi yadvṛttaṃ munisattama|| 72.1||
apanīya tadā viṣṇoḥ siṃharūpaṃ vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
kim anyadakaroddhīmānetadicchāmi veditum|| 72.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
svayoniṃ viṣṇum ānīya devadevo bhavastadā|
mandare sahito devyā vicacāra mahādyutiḥ|| 72.3||
ramyān sa kānanoddeśān gireḥ prasravaṇāni ca|
alaṃcakāra deveśaḥ parisarpan samantataḥ|| 72.4||
vanaprekṣārataṃ devaṃ jñātvā śaṃkaram avyayam|
śarat tatra vasantaśca dvāvṛtū samupasthitau|| 72.5||
tato mahīruhāḥ sarve sarāṃsi ca samantataḥ|
nānāvidhāni puṣpāṇi mumucuḥ sahasā samam|| 72.6||
kamalotpalasaṃchannāḥ ṣaṭpadavrātasevitāḥ|
haṃsasārasasaṃvāsā vāpyastatra manoharāḥ|| 72.7||
gandhāḍhyā jātayaḥ kṣipraṃ babhūvuḥ saha campakaiḥ|
aśokā gandhapuṣpāśca tathā caivātimuktakāḥ|| 72.8||
upatasthuḥ samaṃ devaṃ sarvagandhasukhānilāḥ|
sarvartukusumākīrṇaṃ dṛṣṭvā tadvanam uttamam|| 72.9||
puṣpāṇi ādāya deveśaḥ svayam eva jagatpatiḥ|
alaṃcakāra hṛṣṭātmā devīṃ himagireḥ sutām|| 72.10||
nandīśvaraṃ ca pārśvastham ātmānaṃ ca sureśvaraḥ|
tataḥ praṇamya deveśaṃ pārvatī praṇayādidam|| 72.11||
vacaḥ provāca jananī kṛtsnasya jagato 'avyayā|
yathā me dehajaḥ putro bhavitā govṛṣadhvaja|| 72.12||
tvadvīryastvatprabhāvāśca sarvadevanamaskṛtaḥ|
tathā kuru mahādeva yadi te priyatā mayi|| 72.13||
evam uktastadā devyā devadevastrilocanaḥ|
provācedaṃ mahātejā devyāḥ priyacikīrṣayā|| 72.14||
evaṃ bhavatu deveśe vijñaptiṃ saphalām imām|
kariṣyāmi taveśāni putraste sa bhavedyathā|| 72.15||
śreṣṭhaḥ sarvasureśānāṃ mahāyogabalānvitaḥ|
kṛtsnaṃ jagadidaṃ yasya vaśe sthāsyati bhāmini|| 72.16||
gacchantyā tat tapaḥ kartuṃ varaḥ pūrvam api tvayā|
prārthito hyeṣa putrārthaṃ tenāvaśyaṃ dadāmi te|| 72.17||
evam uktvā tu tau devau girijābhuvaneśvarau|
nandīśena tadā sārdhaṃ vicarantau jagadgurū|| 72.18||
sarvodyānāni paśyantau vindhyam ājagmaturgirim|
athāgamya tu vindhyasya sauvarṇaṃ śikharottamam|| 72.19||
darīkandarasaṃkīrṇaṃ nānānirjharasaṃyutam|
sataḍinmeghasaṃghātaghanīkṛtaśiloccayam|| 72.20||
nānāvṛkṣaśilopetaṃ nānākusumasaṃyutam|
nānākhagaravāmodaṃ hemaratnojjvalaṃ śubham|| 72.21||
mānasaṃ tasya madhye tu puraṃ sṛṣṭvā maharddhimat|
maṇihemamayaṃ divyaṃ devāsuravimohanam|| 72.22||
paramaiśvaryasaṃyuktau yutau viviśatuḥ puram|
nandinaṃ ca tato devī samājñāpayadavyayā|| 72.23||
vatsa nandiṃstathā dvāre tiṣṭhestvaṃ gaṇapeśvara|
viśenneha yathā kaścit sūkṣmo vāyurapi sthitaḥ|| 72.24||
kṛtvā śirasi tām ājñāṃ nandīśo gaṇapādhipaḥ|
abhavaddvāramūlasthaḥ kṛtvā tejo 'atiduḥsaham|| 72.25||
yogayuktau tadā devau parāṃ mūrtiṃ samāsthitau|
kṛtsnasya jagato yonī pārvatībhuvaneśvarau|| 72.26||
tasthatuḥ suciraṃ kālaṃ tanayārthaṃ mahādyutī|
sa na śakyo mayā vaktuṃ brahmaṇā vā mahāmune|| 72.27||
suyogo yo 'abhavaddevyā devadevasya śūlinaḥ|
brahmaṇo madvidhānāṃ ca śreṣṭho 'asau parameśvaraḥ|| 72.28||
avaśyaṃ tu āgame vācyaṃ yathāvṛttaṃ yathāśrutam|
ato vakṣyāmi te vyāsa priyaḥ śiṣyaśca me bhavān|| 72.29||
yogasandhānam āsthāya tayorevaṃ mahāmune|
atītaṃ sthitayordivyaṃ sahasraṃ śaradām abhūt|| 72.30||
tato 'abhavan nimittāni ghorāṇi trāsanāni ca|
cacāla pṛthivī kṛtsnā saśailavanakānanā|| 72.31||
nadyaḥ śoṣaṃ tadā jagmuścukṣubhe saritāṃ patiḥ|
tapano niṣprabhaścāsīdvavāvuṣṇaḥ samīraṇaḥ|| 72.32||
peturulkā mahāghorā diśaścāsan sudāruṇāḥ|
evam utpātavitrastāḥ śubhahetorvasundharā|| 72.33||
jagāma śaraṇaṃ viṣṇuṃ gatvā cārtiṃ nyavedayat|
utpātā dāruṇā deva babhūvurbahavo bhṛśam|| 72.34||
tenātīva samudvignā tvām adya śaraṇaṃ gatā|
atha viṣṇuḥ surān sarvānidam aśrāvayat prabhuḥ|| 72.35||
tato divaukasaḥ sarve bṛhaspatipurogamāḥ|
ekatra saṃgatā bhūtvā cakrurbahuvidhāḥ kathāḥ|| 72.36||
mahābuddhirathāhedaṃ vākyam aṅgirasaḥ sutaḥ|
śrīkaṇṭho bhagavāneṣa devadevastrilocanaḥ|| 72.37||
yukto 'abhūddhimavatputryā tanayārthaṃ mahādyutiḥ|
divyaṃ varṣasahasraṃ tu yogena parameṣṭhinaḥ|| 72.38||
agādyuktasya pārvatyā babhūvurdāruṇāstataḥ|
utpātā jagatastrāsāścintyate kim ihāparam|| 72.39||
gacchāma sahitāḥ sarve stotuṃ bhaktyā vṛṣadhvajam|
yathā ca dehajaḥ putro bhaveddevyāḥ sureśvarāḥ|| 72.40||
vijñāpayāmāsa deveśaṃ tathā śīghram ihāmarāḥ|
tato vaivasvataḥ prāha vacaḥ krodhābhiniḥsṛtam|| 72.41||
kimarthaṃ bhṛśam udvignā bhavantaḥ sarva eva hi|
yadyasau devadevasya tanayo 'asmāsu bhaktimān|| 72.42||
utpatsyati na ca drogdhā tataḥ kṣaṃsyāma taṃ surāḥ|
atha cet karkaśo 'asmāsu drogdhā vā sa bhaviṣyati|| 72.43||
tata enam ahaṃ baddhvā kālapāśena bālakam|
āneṣye svavaśaṃ krūraṃ mṛtyunā sahito 'amarāḥ|| 72.44||
na cet purandaro vajraṃ tasya kṣepsyati mūrdhani|
dvidhā yena kṛto mūḍhaḥ prāṇāṃstyakṣyati dustyajān|| 72.45||
bruvatastasya bahvevaṃ krodhasaṃraktalocanaḥ|
viṣṇuḥ provāca dharmātmā vacāṃsi paramārthavit|| 72.46||
aho tvayā suviśrabdhaṃ procyate bhāskarātmaja|
paramārtham avijñāya krodhasya vaśavartinā|| 72.47||
tanayaḥ kila yaḥ śambhorgirijāyāṃ bhaviṣyati|
sa mūḍha iva yaḥ kaścidbhavitā vaśagastava|| 72.48||
kim asau mānavo 'anyo vā janmamṛtyusamanvitaḥ|
utpatsyati raveḥ putra yena syādvaśagastava|| 72.49||
kālenāparipūrṇena mānavasyāpi bhānuja|
na tvaṃ nāśayitā nāma kimu putrasya śūlinaḥ|| 72.50||
tejo bhagavataḥ śambhoryadbhaviṣyatyanuttamam|
sa kathaṃ vadhyatāṃ yāyāt tava śakrasya vā vibho|| 72.51||
bravīmi vo hitaṃ devāḥ kriyate yadi madvacaḥ|
prayāma sahitāḥ sarve taṃ prasādayituṃ haram|| 72.52||
yo naḥ svayaṃvare datto varastiṣṭhati śaṃkare|
tam eva varayiṣyāmo varam agryaṃ pinākinam|| 72.53||
yathā na dehajo devyāstanayaḥ sambhaviṣyati|
nāsmākam ahitaṃ śambhuḥ putram utpādayiṣyati|| 72.54||
vayam eva sutāḥ sarve śaṃkarasyāgrajā vibhoḥ|
na śakyastapasā draṣṭuṃ na jñānena sureśvarāḥ|| 72.55||
bhaktyā paramayā draṣṭuṃ śakyaḥ syāt sa vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
āgacchadhvaṃ gamiṣyāmo yatra tiṣṭhati śaṃkaraḥ|| 72.56||
parāṃ bhaktiṃ samāsthāya yathā paśyeya śaṃkaram|
hutabhuk caiva no devastatsakāśaṃ pravekṣyati|| 72.57||
sarveṣām eva vijñaptyā surāṇāṃ surasattamāḥ|
iti śrutvā vacastasya viṣṇoramitatejasaḥ|| 72.58||
bṛhaspatipurogāste hṛṣṭātmāno divaukasaḥ|
sādhu sādhviti santuṣṭā vacāṃsi ūcuḥ surottamāḥ|| 72.59||
tato viṣṇusahāyāste gatvā tacchṛṅgam uttamam|
ūcurhutāśanaṃ devaṃ vacaḥ stutipuraḥsaram|| 72.60||
tvam agne sarvadevānāṃ hitakṛt sarvato 'avyayaḥ|
praviśya trāhi naḥ sarvāñchaṃkarāya nivedaya|| 72.61||
tathā kuryāḥ suraśreṣṭha yena nirgamya śaṃkaraḥ|
asmān nirīkṣate devaḥ prahvān bhaktimataḥ sthitān|| 72.62||
ityuktaḥ sa suraiḥ sarvaiḥ pratyuvāca hutāśanaḥ|
akartavyaṃ hi me devā na yuṣmān prati vidyate|| 72.63||
pārvatyā saha saṃyuktaṃ devadeveśvaraṃ param|
na me śaktirharaṃ draṣṭuṃ bhavantaścākulā bhṛśam|| 72.64||
yuṣmadvākyam alaṅghyaṃ ca kṛcchram etadatīva me|
pravekṣye dūtavaddevāḥ kariṣye sāhasaṃ mahat|
ityuktvā sa jagāmāśu bhavanaṃ tat kapardinaḥ|| 72.65||
tatrāpaśyat sthitaṃ dvāre nandinaṃ paramaujasam|
dvāram ākramya tiṣṭhantaṃ dīptapaṭṭiśadhāriṇam|| 72.66||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sa tadā vahniḥ samālokya samantataḥ|
nāsti kaścidihopāyaḥ sūkṣmajantorapi sthite|| 72.67||
praveṣṭum iti saṃcintya tam eva śaraṇaṃ yayau|
nandinaṃ hutabhugdevastuṣṭāva ca kṛtāñjaliḥ|| 72.68||
namo gaṇādhipataye namaścaṇḍāya śūline|
namaḥ senādhipataye namaḥ śarvātmane sadā|| 72.69||
hālāhalāya rudrāya nīlarudrāya vai namaḥ|
namo {}i {}itirudrāya tathaivārdrapaṭāya ca|| 72.70||
namaste svapnarudrāya bhasmarudrāya te namaḥ|
namaḥ śmaśānarudrāya koṭīrudrāya te namaḥ|| 72.71||
namaḥ piṅgalarudrāya rudrādhipataye namaḥ|
namaḥ pramatharudrāya bhūtarudrāya te namaḥ|| 72.72||
virūpākṣāya rudrāya śvetarudrāya te namaḥ|
namaste satataṃ deva namaste satataṃ śiva|| 72.73||
namaste satataṃ saumya namaste bhaktavatsala|
mama bhaktasya deva tvaṃ devānāṃ hitam icchataḥ|| 72.74||
varado bhava nandīśa mā naḥ krodhaṃ kṛthāḥ prabho|
tato nandīśvaraḥ prāha stuvantam analaṃ sthitam|| 72.75||
prītastavānayā vahne bhaktyāhaṃ surasattama|
brūhi kiṃ te priyaṃ deva karavāṇi hutāśana|| 72.76||
atha provāca vahnistaṃ varadaṃ nandinaṃ sthitam|
yadi tuṣṭo 'asi me deva deyo yadi varaśca me|| 72.77||
devakāryeṇa deveśa praveṣṭuṃ dīyatāṃ mama|
bhavanaṃ devadevasya vara eṣo 'astu me vibho|| 72.78||
taṃ nandī pratyuvācedaṃ kṛcchraṃ deyo varo hyayam|
na tamśakṣyasi deveśaṃ draṣṭuṃ tvaṃ yogam āsthitam|| 72.79||
saha devyā maheśānaṃ sraṣṭāraṃ jagato 'avyayam|
tathāpyeṣa mayā tubhyaṃ deya eva varo 'anala|| 72.80||
gaccha sūkṣmataro bhūtvā durālakṣyo hutāśana|
praviśya niṣkrama kṣipramavijñātāgamakriyaḥ|| 72.81||
sa nandinābhyanujñāto jātavedā mudā yutaḥ|
jyotiḥ sūkṣmataro bhūtvā bhāskarasyāṃśunā saha|| 72.82||
praviśya bhavanaṃ śambhormaṇistambham athāviśat|
vāhneyamaṇimadhyasthaṃ stambhaṃ taṃ bhāsayan muhuḥ|| 72.83||
so 'apaśyat tatra deveśaṃ devīṃ ca bhuvaneśvarīm|
tuṣṭāva manasā devau tato 'asau havyavāhanaḥ|| 72.84||
tathā saṃstūyamānaśca prītiṃ devyāśca darśayan|
vīkṣya stambhaṃ haro devīṃ vākyam etadabhāṣata|| 72.85||
eṣa stambhamaṇirdevi bhrājamāna iva priye|
saṃstauti māṃ tvayā sārdhaṃ dadānyasmai varaṃ śubham|| 72.86||
devyuvāca|
evaṃ kuru mahādeva bhaktasyāsya sureśvara|
stuvatastvā mayā sārdhaṃ prayaccha varam uttamam|| 72.87||
devadeva uvāca|
prīto 'ahaṃ maṇimadhyastha bhaktyā te vinayena ca|
brūhi kāryaṃ yatheṣṭaṃ tvaṃ tat sarvaṃ te baviṣyati|| 72.88||
agniruvāca|
devāstvāṃ draṣṭum icchanti bahiṣthā bhuvaneśvara|
bhagavaṃste yathā sarve paśyeyustvāṃ tathā kuru|| 72.89||
devadeva uvāca|
evam astu suraśreṣṭha nirgatya tridivaukasām|
dadāmi darśanaṃ vahne bhavataḥ priyakāmyayā|| 72.90||
tatheti samanujñāto vahnistasmādvinirgataḥ|
devebhyaḥ kāryam āvedya tasthau yogaṃ samāsthitaḥ|| 72.91||
atha niṣkramya bhagavān devadevaḥ pinākdhṛk|
jagāma tvaritaṃ tatra yatra devāḥ samāsate|| 72.92||
atha dṛṣṭvā mahādevaṃ devāḥ sarve vṛṣadhvajam|
praṇemurmūrdhabhirhṛṣṭāstuṣṭuvuśca mudā yutāḥ|| 72.93||
namaḥ sahasranetrāya sahasracaraṇāya ca|
mahatāṃ pataye nityaṃ devānāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 72.94||
namaḥ śmaśānarataye vyāghracarmasuvāsase|
brahmaṇaśca śirohartre viṣṇorvai varadāya vai|| 72.95||
namo dakṣamakhaghnāya namaste tyambakāya ca|
namo bhūtādhipataye pradhānamathanāya ca|| 72.96||
pinākapāṇaye nityaṃ sarvayogātmayogine|
namo nīlaśikhaṇḍāya sapatnīkāya vai namaḥ|| 72.97||
namaḥ kāmeṣvasaktāya kāmasaktāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ sarvāya śarvāya daṇḍine jaṭine namaḥ|
namaḥ sarvātmabhūtāya diśa no yanmanogatam|| 72.98||
evaṃ saṃstūyamāno 'atha sarvaireva surottamaiḥ|
pratyuvāca mahādevastān surān praṇatān sthitān|| 72.99||
parituṣṭo 'asmi bho devā brūta kiṃ pradadāni vaḥ|
punaḥ praṇamya te devāḥ prāhurvacanam uttamam|| 72.100||
yo naḥ svayaṃvare deva varo dattastvayā vibho|
taṃ prārthayāma sahitāstanno dātuṃ tvam arhasi|| 72.101||
devyā ya eṣa putrārthaṃ yogaste bhuvaneśvara|
kṛto 'abdāni bahūni sma taṃ saṃhara namastava|| 72.102||
aśubhāni nimittāni dṛśyante sumahādyute|
pṛthivī duḥsthitā deva vayaṃ ca bhṛśam ākulāḥ|| 72.103||
tenaiṣa na yathā devyā dehe saṃjāyate sutaḥ|
jāyeta ca yathā deva tathā naḥ kartum arhasi|| 72.104||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā devadevo 'abravīdvacas|
mahāneṣa varaḥ sarvaiḥ prārthitaḥ surapuṅgavaiḥ|| 72.105||
tathāpi ca prayacchāmi yuṣmatpriyacikīrṣayā|
mahāntaṃ kiṃ tvidaṃ kālaṃ tejaḥ sandhāritaṃ mayā|| 72.106||
asya prapaśyata sthānam amoghaṃ hyetaduttamam|
athaivam uktā devena te devā munisattama|| 72.107||
babhūvuḥ sahitāstūṣṇīṃ surā brahmapurogamāḥ|
teṣāṃ madhye tadā vahniḥ provāca bhuvaneśvaram|| 72.108||
juhudhyetat paraṃ tejo mayi deva trilokapa|
juhāvāgnau tatastejastadā svīyaṃ paraṃ bhavaḥ|| 72.109||
hutvā tasmiṃstataḥ kṛtsnaṃ tuṣṭo 'abhūt parameśvaraḥ|
varaṃ vṛṇu hutāśa tvam iti provāca śaṃkaraḥ|| 72.110||
tato vahniḥ praṇamyeśaṃ varānabhyarthayadvibhuṃ |
iccheyam etaṃ putraṃ te mama nāmnā prakīrtitam|| 72.111||
śāpasyāham agamyaḥ syāṃ paśyeyaṃ tvāṃ ca nityaśaḥ|
dhārayeyaṃ sukhenaitadutsṛjeyaṃ ca śaṃkara|| 72.112||
sarvabhakṣo 'apyalepaḥ syāṃ pāpaṃ na ca bhavenmama|
mayi devāśca yajñāśca pratiṣṭhāṃ yāntu śūladhṛk|| 72.113||
ahaṃ bhūteśvaraśca syām ahaṃ paśupatiśca ha|
ahaṃ tava tanuḥ syāṃ ca tvanmūrtistvadupāśrayaḥ|| 72.114||
varam icchāmi deveśa dīyamānam imaṃ tvayā|
evam astviti tat sarvaṃ vahnaye pradadau vibhuḥ|| 72.115||
visṛjya ca tato devān devadevo vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
puno viveśa bhavanaṃ devī cainam abhāṣata|| 72.116||
kva gatvā tvam ihāyātaḥ kṣipraṃ tribhuvaneśvara|
kiṃ tadgurutaraṃ kāryaṃ yena nirgatavānasi|| 72.117||
tataḥ provāca deveśaḥ pārvatīṃ ruṣitānanām|
gato 'asmi tvarito devi devairvijñāpitaḥ priye|| 72.118||
bahiḥsthaiḥ padmapatrākṣi bhaktimadbhiḥ suduḥkhitaiḥ|
athovāca tato devī devaṃ sarvajagatpatim|| 72.119||
kathaṃ tvam āgatān deva bahiḥsthāṃstridivaukasaḥ|
jñātavānasi santrastān kenākhyātaṃ ca te vibho|| 72.120||
devadeva uvāca|
praviśya hutabhugdevi maṇistambhaṃ samāsthitaḥ|
nyavedayat stuvan mahyaṃ sarvān devān bahiḥsthitān|| 72.121||
tavaivānujñayā devi tasmai datto varo mayā|
tato bhagavatī kruddhā nandinaṃ prāha pārvatī|| 72.122||
kathaṃ praviṣṭaste vahnirdvārasthasyeha durmate|
tataḥ sāsya bhṛśaṃ kruddhā śravaṇanyastam utpalam|| 72.123||
gṛhītvā vajrasaṃkāśaṃ nandīśāya vyasarjayat|
dvādaśādityasaṃkāśaṃ prajvalat tat tadotpalam|| 72.124||
vadhārthaṃ nandino ghoraṃ prasasāra sphuṭanniva|
hato nandīśvara iti procyotthāya ca śaṃkaraḥ|| 72.125||
bhadraṃ bhavotpala kṣipram ityuktvāgṛhṇadutpalam|
athomāpi tato devī pratyāpattiṃ jagāma ha|| 72.126||
aho bata mahat kaṣṭaṃ kṛtaṃ krodhavaśānmayā|
kathaṃcinna hato nandī mahāgaṇapanāyakaḥ|| 72.127||
tadgṛhītvā tato hastāddevasya śravaṇotpalam|
cikṣepa tvaritaṃ devī bhadraṃ bhavatu te saraḥ|| 72.128||
evam uktvā tataḥ kṣiptaṃ devyā tacchravaṇotpalam|
vindhyapṛṣṭhe sarastatra bahupadmotpalaṃ babhau|| 72.129||
haṃsasārasasaṃkīrṇaṃ cakravākopaśobhitam|
nāmnā bhadrotpalam iti hemaśṛṅgasamīpataḥ|| 72.130||
tatra snātvā naraḥ kṣipraṃ sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
tatrākṣayaṃ sadā dānaṃ pitṛtarpaṇam eva ca|| 72.131||
mṛtaścātra naro yāti nandīśvarasalokatām|
tato devaṃ puno devī vākyam āha gireḥ sutā|| 72.132||
kim ūcustvāṃ surā deva kīdṛśaṃ cārthayan varam|
kathayāmāsa deveśastato devyai vṛṣadhvajaḥ|| 72.133||
devairvijñāpito devi nirgato 'ahaṃ varānane|
devyā ya eṣa putrārthaṃ yogaste bhuvaneśvara|| 72.134||
aśubhānyatra dṛśyante dāruṇāni sahasraśaḥ|
santrastā pṛthivī kṛtsnā vayaṃ ca bhṛśam ākulāḥ|| 72.135||
tenaiṣa na yathā devyā garbhe saṃjāyate sutaḥ|
bhavecca tanayaḥ ślāghyo vara eṣa pradīyatām|| 72.136||
tato 'agnau taddhutaṃ tejo mayā putrārtham īśvari|
sutaste bhavitā śrīmān ṣaṭśirā dvādaśekṣaṇaḥ|| 72.137||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā śaśāpa girijāmarān|
yasmānmama suto dehe nepsitaṃ tairdurātmabhiḥ|
svāsu patnīṣe tasmāt te na prāpsyanti surāḥ sutam|| 72.138||
pṛthivī cāpi saṃmūḍhā macchāpopahatendriyā|
bahūn patīn samāsādya na putraṃ prāpsyate kvacit|| 72.139||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
virarāma tato devī śaptvā devān savāsavān|
kaiṭabhā nāma nāmnā ca puṇyā naikavarapradā|| 72.140||
vindhyasya śikhare haime tatrābhūdgirijā śubhā|
puṇyam āyatanaṃ taddhi śilāṃ ca ramaṇāhvayām|| 72.141||
yo 'abhigacchennaro vyāsa mṛtaḥ sa gaṇapo bhavet|
athājagmuḥ surāḥ sarve sārdhaṃ tatra havirbhujā|| 72.142||
vivarṇāḥ kaśmalopetāḥ sagarbhā lajjayānvitāḥ|
tān dvāḥsthān āgatān nandī śaṃkarāya nyavedayat|| 72.143||
praviśya samanujñātā devam ūcurdivaukasaḥ|
tejo na śaknumaḥ soḍhum idaṃ tribhuvaneśvara|| 72.144||
trāhi naḥ suralokeśa yathā syāma gatajvarāḥ|
andhakaścāsuro 'atyarthaṃ tapyate duścaraṃ tapaḥ|
bhayaṃ ca nastato deva dṛśyate sumahadvibho|| 72.145||
devadeva uvāca|
mā bhīrbhavatu vo devā haniṣyāmyaham andhakam|
yuṣmadarthe parākrāntaṃ hirāṇyākṣasutaṃ varam|| 72.146||
yūyaṃ ca merumadhyasthaṃ vanaṃ yāta suvistṛtam|
nāmnā śaravaṇaṃ nāma puṇyaṃ dvādaśayojanam|| 72.147||
yuṣmākaṃ tatra sambhidya kukṣīn daivatapuṅgavāḥ|
madīyaṃ tat paraṃ tejo nirgamiṣyati dīptimat|| 72.148||
suvarṇatvaṃ ca yāsyanti kukṣayo vaḥ surottamāḥ|
tataste tadvacaḥ śrutvā praṇamya śirasā bhavam|| 72.149||
śrīmantaṃ merum ājagmuḥ śaradhānaṃ ca tacchubham|
yatra teṣāṃ tadā bhittvā kukṣīṃsteṣāṃ nirakramīt|| 72.150||
yugāntānalasaṃkāśaṃ durnirīkṣyaṃ surāsuraiḥ|
meruścaivābhavat kṣipraṃ śrīmānatimanoharaḥ|| 72.151||
sarvaṃ hiraṇmayaṃ cakre tejo māheśvaraṃ param|
vāti gandhavaho divyaḥ sarvartukusumāvahaḥ|| 72.152||
teṣāṃ ca kukṣibhedāste suvarṇatvaṃ paraṃ yayuḥ|
svarge dundubhayo divyā neduḥ svayam anāhatāḥ|| 72.153||
puṣpāṇāṃ vṛṣṭayaḥ petuḥ sugandhīnām anekaśaḥ|
namaskāraiśca bhūtānām adṛśyānām abhūt svanaḥ|| 72.154||
evamādīni paśyantaḥ śṛṇvantaśca surottamāḥ|
gatvā pinākine hṛṣṭāḥ sarvam āvedya suvrata|
preṣitāḥ sthāṇunā jagmuḥ svā/llokān hṛṣitānanāḥ|| 72.155||
śrutvā devairabhihitam idaṃ prītiyuktairvaco 'agryaṃ prītā devī hṛdayamahitā putrajanmapravṛttim|
jñātvā tasthau vibudhavaradā yogamātā vidhātrī tuṣṭiṃ cāgāddhṛdi suraśiraḥspṛṣṭapādāravindā|| 72.156||
iti skandapurāṇe
skandajanmapravṛttirnāma
dvisaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 72.72||

trisaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
andhakaḥ kasya putro 'asau kiṃvīryaḥ kiṃparākramaḥ|
kathaṃ ca nihataḥ saṃkhye sarvam etadvadasva me|| 73.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vyāsa mahābuddhe sarvam etadyathābhavat|
andhakasya purāvṛttaṃ sarvaṃ vakṣyāmi te dvija|| 73.2||
kaśyapasya sutau dityāṃ daityau tau sambabhūvatuḥ|
hiraṇyakaśipurjyeṣṭho hiraṇyākṣastato 'anujaḥ|| 73.3||
jyeṣṭhastatrābhavadrājā hiraṇyakaśipustadā|
tasmin vinihite vīre narasiṃhena dhīmatā|| 73.4||
hiraṇyākṣo 'abhavadrājā sarvadaityanamaskṛtaḥ|
aputraḥ sa tapastepe putrahetoriti śrutiḥ|| 73.5||
sa śaṃkukarṇaṃ samprāpya sindhusāgarasaṃgame|
tapastepe diteḥ putro devaṃ draṣṭuṃ pinākinam|| 73.6||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ tadabhavaddivyaṃ pavitraṃ lokaviśrutam|
śaṃkukarṇaṃ maheśasya kṣetraṃ sarvārthasādhakam|
yat phalaṃ puṇyasampacca tanme vyākhyātum arhasi|| 73.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
purā hi bhagavān devaḥ kapardī nīlalohitaḥ|
sindhusāgaram āgamya lokānugrahahetave|| 73.8||
tapaḥ kartuṃ samārebhe yadacintyaṃ surāsuraiḥ|
daśasvapi tato dikṣu rakṣaṇārthaṃ jagatpatiḥ|| 73.9||
sthāpayāmāsa gaṇapān nikumbhādīn sahasraśaḥ|
śaṃkukarṇaṃ mahādaṃṣṭraṃ sthūlākṣaṃ sthūlanāsikam|| 73.10||
hrasvapādakaraṃ caiva dāritāsyaṃ vibhīṣaṇam|
śārdūlacarmasaṃcchannaṃ dvīpicarmottaracchadam|| 73.11||
śaṃkukarṇam iti khyātaṃ gaṇeśaṃ sumahābalam|
samāhūya samīpaṃ tu bhagavānidam abravīt|| 73.12||
svaistvaṃ gaṇeśvaraiḥ sārdhaṃ na viśeyuryathā surāḥ|
tathā pāhi vanaṃ vatsa yāvadeta vrataṃ mama|| 73.13||
evaṃ sa kṛtvā rakṣāṃ tu mahādevo vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
tapastepe mahat tatra ghoraṃ paramaduścaram|| 73.14||
athājagmuḥ surāstatra sarve śakrapurogamāḥ|
niruddhāḥ śaṃkukarṇena na celuḥ padam agrataḥ|| 73.15||
devā ūcuḥ|
bho gaṇeśā vayaṃ devaṃ śarvam ugraṃ kapardinam|
draṣṭuṃ kāryeṇa samprāptāstanno darśayatānaghāḥ|
ākulāstam apaśyanto naśyāma pramatheśvarāḥ|| 73.16||
śaṃkukarṇa uvāca|
na yuṣmābhiḥ surāḥ śakyo devo draṣṭuṃ kathaṃcana|
tapaḥ kuruta bhadraṃ vastato drakṣyatha śaṃkaram|| 73.17||
devā ūcuḥ|
mā lokānāṃ vināśaḥ syādgaṇeśvara mahādyute|
iti prayaccha no dvāraṃ prasādaṃ kuru naḥ prabho|| 73.18||
śaṃkukarṇa uvāca|
lokā naśyantu yūyaṃ vā na praveśaḥ pradīyate|
vinaṣṭān punareveśaḥ srakṣyate bhuvaneśvaraḥ|| 73.19||
sraṣṭā sa eva bhūtānāṃ sa vināśayitā tathā|
taṃ vinā kaḥ surāḥ śakto lokān nāśayituṃ vibhum|| 73.20||
yacchāma na vayaṃ dvāram ājñā naḥ pārameśvarī|
ta evam uktāḥ saṃcintya jagmurbrahmasadaḥ surāḥ|| 73.21||
tato nivedayāmāsurbrahmaṇaste surottamāḥ|
atha brahmā surān āha mayā saha punaḥ surāḥ|| 73.22||
gacchadhvaṃ gaṇapān yāvat pratyāpattiṃ nayāmi vaḥ|
tataste brahmaṇā sārdhaṃ viṣṇunā ca divaukasaḥ|| 73.23||
tam eva punarājagmustiṣṭhate yatra śaṃkaraḥ||
atha tān punarevāsau rurodha gaṇapeśvaraḥ|| 73.24||
śaṃkukarṇo gaṇādhyakṣastejasā prajvalanniva|
atha brahmā tam āhedaṃ sāntvam arthayutaṃ vacaḥ|| 73.25||
gaṇeśvara na devānāṃ dauṣṭyaṃ kiṃciddhi vidyate|
tava prasādāt paśyantu devā devaṃ vṛṣadhvajam|| 73.26||
śirasā praṇatāstubhyaṃ devāścendrapurogamāḥ|
ahaṃ ca viṣṇunā sārdhaṃ prayācema gaṇeśvara|| 73.27||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā brahmaṇaḥ sa gaṇeśvaraḥ|
kruddhaḥ paṭṭiśam udyamya vacaḥ provāca niṣṭhuram|| 73.28||
na me gurutaro devāḥ praṇāmo bhavatāṃ nvayam|
ājñā garīyasī śambhorna praveśo 'asti kaścana|| 73.29||
pratiṣiddhān kathaṃ brahman niyuktā rakṣaṇāya ca|
īśājñāṃ samatikramya prayacchāma praveśanam|| 73.30||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā gaṇeśasya mahātmanaḥ|
ekāntaṃ prayayau brahmā lajjayā parayānvitaḥ|| 73.31||
devāḥ sarve tato dṛṣṭvā vrīḍāyuktaṃ pitāmaham|
kruddhā manyuparītāṅgā vākyam ūcurgaṇeśvaram|| 73.32||
gaṇādhipa na te lajjā gurum ākrośase katham|
naivaṃ tvāṃ vibruvantaṃ hi kṣaṃsyate vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 73.33||
avamānaṃ punarmaivaṃ tvam asmākaṃ kṛthā gaṇa|
mādya te vayam udyuktā nāśayiṣyāma jīvitam|| 73.34||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā śaṃkukarṇo ruṣānvitaḥ|
vacaḥ provāca saṃkruddhastiryagvīkṣya divaukasaḥ|| 73.35||
guravaḥ kiṃ bhavanto me yena śaṃke 'amarādhipāḥ|
prasādya śaṃkaraṃ yūyaṃ gatā devatvam uttamam|| 73.36||
gaṇabhūtāḥ sureśasya yūyam apyamarottamāḥ|
vayam apyatiyogīśā gaṇapāstasya śūlinaḥ|| 73.37||
samānā yūyam asmākaṃ hīnā vā tridivaukasaḥ|
yasmādvayaṃ sureśānaṃ paśyāmo 'anucarāma ca|| 73.38||
sarvaireva suraistasmādvayaṃ pūjyāḥ sadādhikāḥ|
paśyāmo nirbhayā yūyaṃ praveśaṃ kurutāmarāḥ|| 73.39||
yāvadadya gaṇeśānāṃ balaṃ drakṣyatha dāruṇam|
yadvā balaṃ ca yogaśca yat tapo yaśca vaḥ śramaḥ|| 73.40||
tat sarvaṃ darśayadhvaṃ vai tato drakṣyatha me balam|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā sarve devāḥ sugarvitāḥ|| 73.41||
pragṛhītāyudhāḥ kṣipraṃ śaṃkukarṇaṃ vidudruvuḥ|
teṣām āpatatāṃ vyāsa surāṇāṃ śūramāninām|| 73.42||
balaṃ jagrāha yogena śaṃkukarṇo mahābalaḥ|
nigṛhītabalāste tu sarva eva surottamāḥ|| 73.43||
nāśaknuvan padaṃ dātuṃ tasthuḥ stambhā ivācalāḥ|
nigṛhīteṣu deveṣu viṣṇuḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|| 73.44||
abhidudrāva vegena śaṃkukarṇaṃ gaṇeśvaram|
sa yogena tadā viṣṇordeham astambhayadbalī|| 73.45||
sa yogaṃ punarāsthāya viṣṇuraiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|
yuyudhe śaṃkukarṇena sa cainaṃ pratyayudhyata|| 73.46||
tayostu yogeśvarayoryuktayormunisattama|
babhūva sumahadyuddhaṃ yogenaiva parasparam|| 73.47||
vinigṛhya sa taṃ viṣṇuṃ gaṇeśaḥ śarvavallabhaḥ|
pitaraṃ mama yogena yuyodha paramādbhutaḥ|| 73.48||
sa sūkṣmaṃ yogam āsthāya brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|| 73.49||
tatra tatra sthitaṃ hyagre śaṃkukarṇam avaikṣata|
sa bhūtāni samutsṛjya tanmātrāṇi āviśat prabhuḥ|| 73.50||
indriyāṇyatha tattvāni bhāvāṃścaiva pitāmahaḥ|
tatra tatra sa yogātmā yogaṃ paramam āsthitam|| 73.51||
apaśyat sthūlaśirasaṃ śaṃkukarṇaṃ mahābalam|
athāsminnantare vyāsa devadevasya śūlinaḥ|| 73.52||
divyaṃ varṣasahasraṃ tu prayayau dvādaśātmakam|
samāptaṃ cābhavadvyāsa vrataṃ tasya mahātmanaḥ|| 73.53||
sa samāpte vrate tasmin yugāntāgnisamadyutiḥ|
avaikṣata diśaḥ sarvā jīvayanniva śaṃkaraḥ|| 73.54||
so 'apaśyannigṛhītāṃstān sarvāneva divaukasaḥ|
sāmnaiva sa tadā devaḥ śaṃkukarṇaṃ nyavārayat|| 73.55||
samyagājñā kṛtā vatsa tvayā me gaṇapeśvara|
muñca devānimān sarvān māvamaṃsthā gaṇeśvara|| 73.56||
evaṃ devena samproktaḥ śaṃkukarṇo gaṇādhipaḥ|
vimucya devatāḥ sarvāstasthau devasamīpataḥ|| 73.57||
surā api tadā sarve vrīḍayā parayā yutāḥ|
praṇemurdevadeveśaṃ bhaktyā paramayā vibhum|| 73.58||
tāṃstadā vrīḍitān devaḥ prahasya viditātmavān|
uvāca brahmaṇā sārdhaṃ viṣṇum ābhāṣya susvaram|| 73.59||
gaṇeśvaro 'ayaṃ deveśā macchāsanaparaḥ sadā|
yadanena kṛtaṃ kiṃcidvyetu tadvaḥ surottamāḥ|
kartavyaṃ yacca tadbrūta yadarthaṃ yūyam āgatāḥ|| 73.60||
brahmovāca|
śaṃkukarṇo hyayaṃ śrīmān gaṇeśo yena no balam|
hataṃ yogena deveśa varo 'asmai sampradīyatām|
asmabhyaṃ parato dadyāḥ sadā darśanam ātmanaḥ|| 73.61||
devadeva uvāca|
asyaivedaṃ bhavennāmnā pavitraṃ lokaviśrutam|
śaṃkukarṇam iti khyātaṃ tathā sthūleśvaraṃ śubham|| 73.62||
samantādyojanamitaṃ sarvatīrthasamanvitam|
sarvayajñaphalairjuṣṭaṃ sarvadānaphalairyutam|| 73.63||
yo 'atrāgatya caruṃ kṛtvā māṃ yatnenārcayiṣyati|
ahorātropavāsena mama lokaṃ sa yāsyati|| 73.64||
yat kiṃcinniyamaṃ kṛtvā yo 'atra saṃvatsaraṃ vaset|
sa yogaṃ paramaṃ prāpya śaṃkukarṇasamo bhavet|| 73.65||
yaśca prāṇāniha kṣetre tyajenniyamam āsthitaḥ|
sa dehabhedam āsādya mahāgaṇapatirbhavet|| 73.66||
pitR̥ṇām akṣayaṃ śrāddham iha dattaṃ bhaviṣyati|
yūyaṃ caiśvaryasampannāstapoyogabalānvitāḥ|| 73.67||
nityaṃ drakṣyatha māṃ devāḥ prayāta vigatajvarāḥ|
tato devo varaṃ dattvā devebhyaḥ prabhurīśvaraḥ|| 73.68||
prakāmaṃ darśanaṃ nityaṃ tatraivāntaradhīyata|
gate tasmin mahādeve brahmā suravarairvṛtaḥ|| 73.69||
tatra liṅgaṃ pratiṣṭhāpya cakre tīrthānyanekaśaḥ|
daśāśvamedhikaṃ tīrthaṃ puṇyaṃ pañcāśvamedhikam|| 73.70||
surāṇāṃ caiva tīrthāni kṛtvā svabhavanaṃ yayau|
etat te kathitaṃ vyāsa sindhusāgarasaṃgame|| 73.71||
paraṃ bhagavataḥ sthānaṃ pavitraṃ lokaviśrutam|
siddhacāraṇasaṃkīrṇam apsarogaṇasevitam|| 73.72||
bahupuṣpaphalopetaṃ sadā vihaganāditam|
tasmin gatvā vane vyāsa hiraṇākṣaḥ pratāpavān|| 73.73||
putrahetostapastepe dhyāyamānastrilocanam|
atha devastadā gatvā sagaṇo vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 73.74||
ramyaṃ himagireḥ śṛṅgaṃ mainākam iti viśrutam|
tasthau paramayogīśaḥ paraṃ brahma sanātanam|| 73.75||
tasyāgatya tadā devīṃ saṃsthitā pṛṣṭhataḥ śanaiḥ|
karābhyāṃ padmatulyābhyāṃ netre śambhornyamīlayat|| 73.76||
jānīte neti saṃcintya krīḍārthaṃ himavatsutā|
atha tasmin kṣaṇe vyāsa jagadandham ajāyata|| 73.77||
apradṛśyaṃ hi tamasā tathābhūtaṃ purā yathā|
atha devastadā dṛṣṭvā tṛtīyaṃ netram avyayam|| 73.78||
lalāṭe 'asṛjadūrdhvasthaṃ yugāntāgnisamaprabham|
tejasā tasya netrasya sa girirbhasmasādabhūt|| 73.79||
pārvatī pitaraṃ dṛṣṭvā tathā dagdhaṃ pinākinā|
apanīya karau tasthau viṣaṇnā patipārśvataḥ|| 73.80||
atha devastadā dṛṣṭvā viṣaṇṇavadanām umām|
saumyena cakṣuṣāpaśyacchailaṃ taṃ punareva tu|| 73.81||
sa tathā dṛṣṭamātrastu punaḥ paurāṇiko 'abhavat|
prakṛtisthaṃ punardṛṣṭvā devī pitaram avyayam|
praṇamyovāca bhartāraṃ hṛṣitāsyā girīndrajā|| 73.82||
śaila eṣa tvayā deva kimarthaṃ bhasmasātkṛtaḥ|
kimarthaṃ prakṛtisthaśca punareva kṛtaḥ prabho|| 73.83||
tasyāstadvacanaṃ śrutvā provāca parameśvaraḥ|
locane me tvayā devi yasmin kāle nimīlite|| 73.84||
andhāḥ samabhava/llokāstadā sarve tamovṛtāḥ|
prakāśārthaṃ tato devi netram etanmayā kṛtam|| 73.85||
lalāṭe sumahadyena dagdho 'ayam acalottamaḥ|
tvāṃ ca dīnāṃ pitṛvadhādupalakṣya tataḥ śubhe|| 73.86||
praiyārthaṃ tava suśroṇi prakṛtisthaḥ punaḥ kṛtaḥ|
asmiṃśca tamasā graste loke tīvreṇa sarvataḥ|| 73.87||
utpanno 'andhaḥ prabhāveṇa mama devi tathaiva ca|
tapyamānāya dāsyāmi hiraṇyākṣāya taṃ sutam|| 73.88||
evam uktvā sa bhagavān pragṛhyāndhaṃ gaṇairvṛtaḥ|
sindhusāgaram āgamya hiraṇyākṣam uvāca ha|| 73.89||
paśya māṃ tvaṃ diteḥ putra cakṣurdivyaṃ dadāmi te|
śarvo 'aham āgato daitya varaṃ brūhi yathepsitam|| 73.90||
sa protthāya hiraṇyākṣaḥ praṇamya śirasā bhavam|
varaṃ samprārthayaddevaṃ putraṃ datsveti satvaram|| 73.91||
tam uvāca suraśreṣṭhaḥ śirasā pādayornatam|
ayaṃ te 'asuraśārdūla putraḥ putraśatāgrajaḥ|| 73.92||
māvajñām andha ityasya kuryāstvam asurādhipa|
bhavitā ye mahāneṣa tapovīryabalānvitaḥ|| 73.93||
na kasyacit tvayaṃ vadhyo matto 'anyasya bhaviṣyati|
tataḥ sa bhagavān devastasmai dattvā sutaṃ śubham|| 73.94||
jagāma śikharaṃ ramyaṃ mainākaṃ punareva tu|
ādāyāndhaṃ punaḥ so 'api hiraṇyākṣo mahāsuraḥ|| 73.95||
svam aśmakapuraṃ yātvā bhāryām āha manasvinīm|
ayaṃ tubhyaṃ suto devi datto bhagavatā svayam|| 73.96||
saṃvarddhayainaṃ yogena mā pramādaṃ kṛthāḥ kvacit|
tasyāḥ snehena taṃ dṛṣṭvā stanābhyāṃ prasnutaṃ payaḥ|| 73.97||
saṃvardhyamānaḥ kālena so 'andhakaḥ samavarddhata|
yadā tu yauvanaṃ prāptastadaivaṃ samacintayat|| 73.98||
dhigjīvitaṃ mamāndhasya mṛtyureva varo mama|
yo 'aham andho na paśyāmi gṛhasambandhibāndhavān|| 73.99||
dhanyāste puruṣā loke ye svayaṃ yāntyaviklavāḥ|
dṛṣṭvā dṛṣṭvā mukhān bandhūn ābhāṣya hi yathāsukham|| 73.100||
kāryaṃ bhavecca loṣṭena tṛṇenātha śavena vā|
na mayānugṛhītena dhiṅmām aśubhakāriṇam|| 73.101||
sutasnehādayaṃ daityaḥ sadā māṃ rakṣate pitā|
hantavyaṃ na vihantyeṣa koṣakṣayakaraṃ hi mām|| 73.102||
nāyaṃ snehena saṃmūḍho jānātīmāṃ mama vyathām|
aham eva kariṣyāmi yat kāryaṃ buddhimattamaiḥ|| 73.103||
tapo mahat samāsthāya cakṣuṣmān bhavitā hyaham|
sa evaṃ pariniścintya bahudhāndhaḥ subuddhimān|| 73.104||
āmantrya sahitaṃ mātrā pitaraṃ taṃ praṇamya ca|
jagāma tapase dhīmān saṃkalpya kṛtaniścayaḥ|| 73.105||
pitrā śokapariplutekṣaṇamukhenāyāsakhinnātmanā
tattīvrādhṛtikhedadṛṣṭivirahaprakṣveḍito 'andhaḥ śvasan
iti skandapurāṇe 'andhakopākhyāne
tapaḥprayāṇaṃ nāma
trisaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 73.73||

catuḥsaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha gatvā sa viprendra hiraṇyākṣasutastadā|
gaṅgādvāraṃ śubhadvāraṃ tapovanam anuttamam|| 74.1||
divyaṃ kanakhalaṃ nāma yatra hairaṇvatī nadī|
vṛkṣāḥ kanakhalā yatra sarva eva hi kāñcanāḥ|| 74.2||
yatra dakṣaḥ purā yajñam ayajaddaivataiḥ saha|
mahādevena yatrāsya yajño vinihataḥ purā|| 74.3||
tatrāsau devam abhyarcya snātaḥ prayatamānasaḥ|
namaskṛtvā daivatebhya idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 74.4||
andhaka uvāca|
ye 'asmiṃstapovane devā bhūtāni vividhāni ca|
sarvāṃstāñcharaṇaṃ yāmi tapaḥsiddhiṃ diśantu me|| 74.5||
adyaprabhṛti kartāsmi tapa ugraṃ suduścaram|
varān yenāpnuyām iṣṭān mṛtyuṃ vā prāṇanāśanam|| 74.6||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktvā tu tataḥ pārāśarya mahābalaḥ|
saṃvatsaraṃ vāyubhakṣo babhūva klamavarjitaḥ|| 74.7||
tathā triṣavaṇasnāyī juhvāno 'agnīṃstathaiva ca|
devārcanarataścaiva japahomaparastathā|| 74.8||
varṣe varṣe tu sampūrṇe svāṅgādutkṛṣya kārṣikam|
piśitasya tadā bhāgaṃ juhāvāgnau mahāsuraḥ|| 74.9||
evaṃ tasyāgamaddivyaṃ sahasraṃ munisattama|
juhvataḥ svāni māṃsāni varṣāṇāṃ pratyahaṃ tadā|| 74.10||
so 'asuraḥ śaṃkhahārāmbusudhākundendupāṇḍaraḥ||
babhūvāsthisirāśeṣaḥ kevalaṃ tapasi sthitaḥ|| 74.11||
sa tena tapasā yukto bhāskaraṃ niṣprabhaṃ tadā|
somaṃ ca grahatārābhiḥ saha cakre 'amitātmavān|| 74.12||
sa eva bhāskaro yadvat prakāśayati tejasā|
aśoṣayat palvalāni nadīkūpasarāṃsi ca|| 74.13||
pavanaṃ stambhayāmāsa so 'andhakastapasā tadā|
vyomni siddhā na gacchanti vimānāni ca petire|| 74.14||
tasya tat tapaso rūpaṃ dṛṣṭvā vighnaśatānyuta|
akarot sahasā śakro vikriyāṃ na ca so 'anvagāt|| 74.15||
tato brahmā tam abhyetya provācāndhakadānavam|
mahāsura tapo ghoraṃ tvayā taptaṃ mahābala|
tuṣṭo 'asmi te mahābāho cakṣuṣmān bhava suvrata|| 74.16||
śarīraṃ prakṛtiṃ yātu yathāpūrvaṃ ca te 'asura|
brūhi cānyaṃ varaṃ bhūyo yaste manasi saṃsthitaḥ|| 74.17||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa cakṣuṣmāṃstadā bhūtvā śarīreṇākṣatena ca|
uvāca praṇataḥ sākṣādbrahmāṇaṃ lokabhāvanam|| 74.18||
andhaka uvāca|
bhagavan yadi tuṣṭo 'asi yadi me caritaṃ tapaḥ|
apratidvandvatāṃ saṃkhye daivatebhyaḥ pitāmaha|| 74.19||
mahābalatvaṃ māyāśca tathā cāmaratām api|
etadicchāmi deveśa yadi tvaṃ varado mama|| 74.20||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā prahasya bhagavān vibhuḥ|
hiraṇyākṣasutaṃ prāha punareva vacaḥ śubham|| 74.21||
amaratvaṃ na daityasya dadāmi ditinandana|
sāntaraṃ tu bhavet tat te svayam evottaraṃ vada|| 74.22||
andhaka uvāca|
yā strī syāllokamātā vai praṇameyaṃ na tāṃ yadi|
tadā syānmama mṛtyustu mṛtyuhīno 'anyathā hyaham|| 74.23||
brahmovāca|
evam etadbhavatu te tvayā proktaṃ yadadya vai|
andhako bhava nāmnā tvaṃ loke khyātiṃ ca yāsyasi|| 74.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā sa bhagavānandhakaṃ devakaṇṭakam|
jagāma svaṃ tadāvāsaṃ virarāmāndhakaśca saḥ|| 74.25||
sa gaṅgāmbhobhirāplutya devam iṣṭvā yathāvidhi|
agniṃ hutvā tato dhīmānanumānya tapovanam|
sahāyaiḥ saha daityendro jagāma piturantikam|| 74.26||
sa hṛṣṭacetāstapasā mahābalo vivṛddhakāmaḥ suraśatrutoṣaṇaḥ|
pituḥ sakāśaṃ punareva dīptimānagacchaddhūtabalāhakopamaḥ|| 74.27||
iti skandapurāṇe 'andhakavaralābho nāma
catuḥsaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 74.74||

pañcasaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
so 'aṣṭābhirdānavaiḥ sārdhaṃ gatvā tatpuram antike|
nivedayāmāsa pituḥ kṛtārtho 'andhaka āgataḥ|| 75.1||
priyākhyātustato vyāsa hiraṇyākṣo 'asureśvaraḥ|
dadau ratnānyanekāni tathā kāmānabhīpsitān|| 75.2||
svayaṃ rājā tadā sarvaiḥ suhṛdbhiḥ saha vāhanaiḥ|
saha strībhiryayau tūrṇaṃ somastārāgaṇairiva|| 75.3||
sa gatvā nātidūre 'atha vane sāśokacampake|
āsasāda sutaṃ śrīmān somo budham ivāparam|| 75.4||
kṛtārthaṃ sa sutaṃ dṛṣṭvā tuṣṭo 'abhūddānaveśvaraḥ|
snehāt sa taṃ pariṣvajya mūrdhnyupāghrāya cāsakṛt|| 75.5||
kathaṃ kena ca kālena ke ca labdhā varāstvayā|
pṛṣṭhaḥ sa kathayāmāsa yathāvṛttam aśeṣataḥ|| 75.6||
tasya tadvaradānaṃ ca tathā māhātmyam eva ca|
śrutvā te 'asuraśārdūlāḥ praṇeduḥ sāgarā iva|| 75.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastaṃ ratham āropya hiraṇyākṣo 'andhakaṃ sutam|
suhṛdbhistaiḥ sahaivāśu praviveśa svakaṃ puram|| 75.8||
sa putrasahito bhāti daityaḥ sampūrṇamānasaḥ|
caran rāśim ivādityo yathā saha śanaiscaraḥ|| 75.9||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ praviśya daityendraḥ suhṛdvargam uvāca saḥ|
adhvaryuriva sānnāyye yathānyānṛtvijaḥ sthitān|| 75.10||
hiraṇyākṣa uvāca|
śṛṇudhvaṃ yadidānīṃ me kṛtyaṃ hṛdi cirasthitam|
kartavyaṃ saha sarvaistu yuṣmābhirbhīmavikramaiḥ|| 75.11||
mayā manīṣitaṃ pūrvaṃ kṛtakṛtya ihāgate|
andhake nagare 'asmin vai kartāhaṃ kaumudīm iti|| 75.12||
makhaghnasya ca devasya devarātriṃ mahāprabhām|
kariṣyāmīti tat sarvaṃ kriyatām aviśaṅkayā|| 75.13||
ghuṣyatāṃ nagara hyasmiṃścatvareṣu sabhāsu ca|
kaumudīdivasānaṣṭau sapta caiva mamājñayā|| 75.14||
tāvadeva ca devasya santu me devarātrayaḥ|
suhṛdo ye ca daityendrā dānavāśca mahābalāḥ|| 75.15||
sarvāsu dikṣu te 'apīha samāyāntu ramantu ca|
asmatpakṣe ca ye viprāḥ śukraprabhṛtayaḥ śubhāḥ|| 75.16|
nāgā rakṣāṃsi yakṣāśca gandharvā manujāstathā|
te 'api sarve samāyāntu ramantu ca mayā saha|| 75.17||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā daityendrā hiraṇyākṣeṇa dhīmatā|
tathā cakrustadā sarvaṃ yathoktam amaradviṣā|| 75.18||
dūtān sampraiṣayan kṣipraṃ daityānāṃ dānavaiḥ saha|
tathānyeṣāṃ ca pakṣāṇām ātmanaḥ śaktinandana|| 75.19||
nimantrayati vo rājā hiraṇyākṣo mahābalaḥ|
suhṛdvargaistu sahitā gacchadhvaṃ taṃ didṛkṣavaḥ|| 75.20||
ghaṇṭikaścāhatairvastrairveṣṭitaḥ suvibhūṣitaḥ|
ārūḍhaḥ pāṇḍaraṃ mattaṃ gajaṃ samavaghoṣayat|| 75.21||
rājā jayati daityendro hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
hatā daityadviṣaḥ sarve danavānāṃ ca śatravaḥ|| 75.22||
jayāya ditiputrāṇām ādityānāṃ bhayāya ca|
prātaḥprabhṛti rājā va ājñāpayati kaumudīm|| 75.23||
devarātriṃ ca devasya rudrasya suranāśanīm|
susaṃmṛṣṭopaliptābhī rathyābhiḥ kriyatāṃ puram|| 75.24||
vāsobhirahataiḥ sarve bhavantu puravāsinaḥ|
sragviṇaḥ saśiraḥsnātā dattabhuktā yathākramam|| 75.25||
gāyantu gāyanāścaiva nṛtyantu naṭanartakāḥ|
ucchriyantāṃ patākāśca gṛhavīthyāpaṇeṣu ca|| 75.26||
gṛhāṇi copaliptāni nityam eva bhavantu ca|
puṣpaprakarajuṣṭāni dhūpairnānāvidhairapi|| 75.27||
sragdāmavanti sarvāṇi vanamālākulāni ca|
brāhmaṇāścaiva bhojyantāṃ kriyantāṃ vācāni ca|| 75.28||
brahmaghoṣāśca sarvatra puṇyāhodīraṇāni ca|
dīparātrau ca sarvatra rājamārge gṛheṣu ca|| 75.29||
anantarāḥ kriyantāṃ vai pracurasnehavarttayaḥ|
taruṇāḥ saha yoṣidbhiḥ samantāt paryaṭantu ca|| 75.30||
ramamāṇā hasantaśca gāyanto nṛttasevinaḥ|
bhāṇḍavādyāni vādyantāṃ nṛtyantāṃ daityayoṣitaḥ|| 75.31||
mahādevasya pūjāṃ ca gandhapuṣpādikīṃ śubhām|
upahārāṃśca vividhān snapanāni mahānti ca|| 75.32||
valayaḥ puṣkalāścaiva bhakṣyabhojyairalaṃkṛtāḥ|
dīpāṃśca vividhākārān pānāni ca rasāṃstathā|| 75.33||
phalāni ca vicitrāṇi māṃsapakvam anūpakam|
suvarṇamaṇictrāṇi īśvarāya prayacchata|| 75.34||
vaddhyantāṃ paśavaścātra bhojyantāṃ dvijasattamāḥ|
yo na kuryādidaṃ sarvaṃ puravāsī janaḥ kvacit|
pātayet tasya śārīraṃ rājā daṇḍaṃ mahāyaśāḥ|| 75.35||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa ghoṣayitvā tu ghāṇṭiko hastipṛṣṭhataḥ|
jagāma svagṛhaṃ bhūyaḥ kaumudī cābhyavartata|| 75.36||
yathoktaṃ tat tadā sarvam akurvata pure janāḥ|
rājāpi saṃyataḥ snātaḥ śuciḥ prayatamānasaḥ|| 75.37||
divase divase vyāsa snapayāmāsa yatnavān|
pañcagavyena śuddhena tailena ca sugandhinā|| 75.38||
kṣīreṇa sarpiṣā dadhnā rasaiśca bahubhiḥ śubhaiḥ|
puṣpaiḥ phalaiśca bījaiśca ratnaiścādbhiḥ samanvitaiḥ|| 75.39||
bhasmanā gandhayuktena udakena sugandhinā|
ekaikasya svayaṃ rājā ghaṭānāṃ daśabhiḥ śataiḥ|| 75.40||
divase divase vyāsa tryambakaṃ so 'abhyasecayet|
gandhaiḥ puṣpaiśca dhūpaiśca japyairbalibhireva ca|| 75.41||
pūjayitvā tato rājā viprānanyānabhojayat|
sa kṛtvā paśubhirmedhyai ratnairmaṇibhireva ca|| 75.42||
baliśayyāsanādyaiśca stūyamāno gṛhān yayau|
tathaivānye 'api daityendrāḥ so 'andhakaśca mahābalaḥ|| 75.43||
cakruḥ sarve muniśreṣṭha yathā rājā tathaiva te|
andhakaṃ sa gṛhītvā tu hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|| 75.44||
padbhyām apātayadvyāsa rudrasyedam udāharan|
eṣa devaḥ sadā putra tavāstu sumukhaḥ prabhuḥ|| 75.45||
asmin bhaktistvayā kāryā bhāvitā parameśvare|
eṣa vandyaśca pūjyaśca ato nāsti paro guruḥ|
pūjayethāḥ sadaivainaṃ bhaktitaḥ parameśvaram|| 75.46||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktvā praṇipatya śaṃkaraṃ mahāsuraḥ so 'asuradānaveśvaraḥ|
jagāma dhīmān punareva nirvṛto niveśanaṃ devapatiryathā svakam|| 75.47||
iti skandapurāṇe
kaumudīmahotasvo nāma
pañcasaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 75.75||

ṣaṭsaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha tasyāṃ saha strībhiḥ kaumudyāṃ daityadānavāḥ|
remire raktamanaso devāḥ svargagatā iva|| 76.1||
tatra kācicchubhāpāṅgī padmaṃ divyaṃ mukhopari|
mukhāravindatrāṇārthaṃ dadau somabhayādiva|| 76.2||
aparā caraṇenaitya priyaṃ matābhyatāḍayat|
śītāṃśuriva pādena vikacaṃ śaradambujam|| 76.3||
aparā rājamārgāṇām anabhijñāḥ kulastriyaḥ|
sphāṭikopacitāṃ bhūmiṃ dṛṣṭvā muñcanti pādukām|| 76.4||
utkṛṣya vasanaṃ cānyā viprendra jalaśaṅkayā|
rājamārgeṣu gacchanti dṛṣṭvā maṇicitāṃ bhuvam|| 76.5||
kācit priyeṇa santyaktā raktenānyena nirgatā|
gṛhāccandrāṃśubhiḥ spṛṣṭā papāta madanālasā|| 76.6||
patitaiva ca sā somam uvācedaṃ kulāṅganā|
bhūyo māṃ tvaṃ karaistīkṣṇairdahase nalinīm iva|| 76.7||
sūryeṇa kila dagdhāni jīvayasyauṣadhāni ha|
madanena kathaṃ dagdhāṃ na jīvayasi māṃ dṛḍham|| 76.8||
kāścidramaṇyo dolāsu dolayantyaḥ parastriyaḥ|
jalacandra ivābhānti vīcicañcalamūrtayaḥ|| 76.9||
kecidgāyanti sahitāḥ strībhirdaityā mahābalāḥ|
gandharvā nandanayane apsarobhiryathā saha|| 76.10||
rājamārgaḥ kvacidbhāti strībhirbahvībhirāvṛtaḥ|
yathā nabhasi citro 'asau divyo devapathaḥ śubhaḥ|| 76.11||
kvacinnūpurakāñcīnāṃ kokilānāṃ ca nisvanaḥ|
babhau śrotrasukhaḥ śrotuḥ kalāmadanadīpanaḥ|| 76.12||
kvacidramaṇaraktānāṃ strīṇāṃ vyāsa priyaiḥ saha|
hṛdayavyākulakaraḥ śrūyate madhuraḥ svaraḥ|| 76.13||
evaṃ samabhavadvyāsa bahucitraḥ sa utsavaḥ|
dānavānāṃ tadā prītisaukhyaviśrambhavardhanaḥ|| 76.14||
tasminnuparate bhūyaḥ pūrvavat sampratiṣṭhate|
prakṛtisthe jane vyāsa dānavāste samāgatāḥ|| 76.15||
viviśurbhīmasaṃhlādāḥ sabhāṃ divyāṃ manoramām|
jāmbūnadamayastambhāṃ vajravaidūryavedikām|| 76.16||
muktādāmāvalambādhyāṃ sragdāmottamabhūṣitām|
vajravaidūryanīlendramahānīlāmrapallavaiḥ|| 76.17||
lohitaiḥ sphāṭikaiścaiva tathā marakatairapi|
divyajālopasannaddhāṃ kiṅkiṇīcitraśobhitām|| 76.18||
bahupuṣpaphalaiścaiva sarvakāmapradairdrumaiḥ|
upetāṃ dīrghikābhiśca bahuśayyāsanāṃ śubhām|| 76.19||
aklamāṃ bahuniṣyandāṃ sarvaduḥkhavivarjitām|
sarvakāmasamṛddhāṃ ca bahustrīpuruṣākulām|| 76.20||
viviśustāṃ sabhāṃ divyāṃ daityā darpasamāvṛtāḥ|
prahlādaścānuhlādaśca sinirvāṣkala eva ca|| 76.21||
virocano baliścaiva baliputrāśca viśrutāḥ|
sahasrāṇi daśa dve ca yeṣāṃ śreṣṭho mahābalaḥ|| 76.22||
bāṇo nāma mahāmāyo rājā bāhusahasradhṛk|
bāṇasya putrā ye cānye sahasrāṇi daśaiva ca|| 76.23||
muro dhamuṣumuṇḍaśca (?) vipracittiśca dānavaḥ|
kālo hayaśirāścaiva sambaraḥ kālasambaraḥ|| 76.24||
viśrutaścendradamanaḥ kālanemī ca dānavaḥ|
tathā sundanisundau ca vipākaḥ pāka eva ca|| 76.25||
rāhuśca śataketuśca dhvajastāraḥ satārakaḥ|
mahiṣo dundubhiścaiva kālakaśca mahābalaḥ|| 76.26||
andhakaśca tathāṭiśca bakaḥ śarabha eva ca|
svarbhānurvṛṣaparvā ca madhuḥ kaiṭabha eva ca|| 76.27||
mahākāyaḥ śatānandaḥ śatadundubhireva ca|
kārttasvanaśca hastī ca balo naraka eva ca|| 76.28||
dhvāṅkṣo mūkelvalau cāpi vātāpī sāsṛpuñjikaḥ|
kaṇḍalaścaiva mīḍhaśca durlomā caiva viśrutaḥ|| 76.29||
dhundhuśca śatamāyaśca śatavārtto 'atha duḥsahaḥ|
candrasūryau naraścaiva devāntakanarāntakau|| 76.30||
brahmahā yajñahā caiva ilvalas (?) pilvakastathā|
mayaśca dānavaśreṣṭho mayaputrāśca viśrutāḥ|| 76.31||
teṣām aṣṭau sahasrāṇi sarve ca kṛtaniśacayāḥ|
vṛtraśca dānavaśreṣṭho namucirbhajahastathā|| 76.32||
śatodaraśca vyaṃsaśca tāthāyaśca (?) hradodaraḥ|
keśī tathā pralambaśca kabandho dhenukaśca ha|| 76.33||
hālo gārgyaśirāścaiva kuśaḥ śambhustathaiva ca|
tathā gaganamūrdhā ca sālukaḥ śālva eva ca|| 76.34||
meghanādaśca vikhyāto mahānādastathaiva ca|
kharo 'atha khararomā ca sūcīlomā ca dānavaḥ|| 76.35||
parigho 'aparighaścaiva daṇḍaḥ kāśyapa eva ca|
dundubhiśca mahākāyaḥ saiṃhikeyaśca yo gaṇaḥ|| 76.36||
tathā hālāhalaścaiva andhakāraka eva ca|
paulomāḥ ṣaṣṭisāhasrāḥ kālakeyāśca viśrutāḥ|
kālakañjāḥ sahasrāṇi aṣṭau te devakaṇṭakāḥ|| 76.37||
nivātakavacānāṃ ca tisraḥ koṭyo mahābalāḥ|
tā eva gaṇitāḥ sarvāḥ koṭyaḥ ṣaṣṭiḥ suradviṣām|| 76.38||
tatpakṣān varjayitvā tu manuṣyān pannagānapi|
rākṣasāṃśca piśācāṃśca yakṣān pakṣina eva ca|
teṣām api tadā vyāsa koṭyo viṃśatisaṃmitāḥ|| 76.39||
te tāṃ sabhāṃ samāviśya sarve darpāt suradviṣaḥ|
savidyusulkā bhānti sma prāvṛḍjaladharā iva|| 76.40||
te svananta ivāmbhodāḥ sadhūmā iva parvatāḥ|
mahiṣā iva nardantaḥ ketavo 'anāgatā iva|| 76.41||
utpātā iva nirmuktāḥ saviṣā iva pannagāḥ|
gajā iva ca saṃmattāḥ pavanā iva vegitāḥ|| 76.42||
surāṇāṃ viprakārārthaṃ tasthurāpūrya tāṃ sabhām|
atha gatvā sabhāpālo rājānam idam abravīt|| 76.43||
sukhāsīnaṃ tadā vyāsa siṃhāsanagataṃ yuvā|
praṇamya śirasā pūrvaṃ jānubhyām avaniṃ gataḥ|| 76.44||
baddhāñjalipuṭaḥ samyagvācā ślakṣaṇapadākṣaram|
svāmī jayatu sarveṣām asurāṇāṃ jayāvahaḥ|| 76.45||
prahlādādyāḥ sabhāṃ sarve vipracittipurogamāḥ|
prāptā viditam astveva yadanyat kartum arhasi|| 76.46||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ suradviṣaḥ śrutvā sarvān prāptān sabhāṃ tadā|
uttasthau sahasā rājā śakraketurivotsave|| 76.47||
sa kirīṭī mahādaṃṣṭro muñjakeśo mahāhanuḥ|
ākarṇāddāritāsyaśca mahācchatraśirāstathā|| 76.48||
ājānubāhurvṛttākṣaḥ piṅgākṣaścorddhvaromavān|
vajrasaṃhananaścaiva mahāyogī mahābalaḥ|| 76.49|| °bala Bh
kirīṭenāti sambhāti savitrevodayastathā|
hāravaryāṅkitoraskaḥ sabalāka ivāmbudaḥ|
saputraḥ prayayau vyāsa himavāniva mūrtimān|| 76.50||
sa tāṃ tadā dānavarājasattamo vicitraratnāṃśuparītakuṇḍalaḥ|
sabhāṃ viveśāsuradaityapuṅgavaiḥ samāvṛtāṃ dyām uditairgrahairiva|| 76.51||
iti skandapurāṇe
hiraṇyākṣasya sabhāpraveśo nāma
ṣaṭsaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 76.76||

ṣaṭsaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa gatvā tāṃ sabhāṃ vyāsa apaśyaddaityadānavān|
prāvṛṭkāle 'ambudān mattān yathendraḥ samupasthitān|| 77.1||
tasya praviṣṭasya tadā sarve eva suradviṣaḥ|
jayeti cakrurutthāya vedā iva pitāmaham|| 77.2||
mottiṣṭhateti tān sarvānavocadasurādhipaḥ|
māyāpañcakam āsādya bhogī vāyudharāniva|| 77.3||
sa teṣām agrato bhāti hiraṇyākṣo mahāsuraḥ|
madhye kalabhavṛndānāṃ yathā matto mahāgajaḥ|| 77.4||
tato jāmbūnade divye upaviṣṭo varāsane|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 77.5||
bhāti siṃhāsanāsīnaḥ sa rājā suravidviṣām|
meruśṛṅgam ivāsādya sabalāko mahāmbudaḥ|| 77.6||
babhūvurupaviṣṭāśca tūṣṇīm evāsurāstadā|
sisṛkṣavo jalaṃ kāle nīlāmbhodā ivonnatāḥ|| 77.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa teṣām iṅgitaṃ jñātvā kālaṃ ca suratāpanaḥ| teṣāṃmiṅgitaṃ Bh typo
hiraṇyākṣaḥ svayaṃ rājā tānuvāca suradviṣaḥ|| 77.8||
yūyaṃ sarve mahāmāyāḥ śṛṇudhvaṃ saṃyatāḥ samam|
kālaprāptaṃ ca pathyaṃ ca śiṣyā iva gurorvacaḥ|| 77.9||
mama bhrātā priyo hi āsījjyeṣṭhaḥ pūjyo yathā pitā|
hiraṇyakaśipuu rājā mahātmā satyasaṃgaraḥ|| 77.10||
dhārmikaśca vadānyaśca yajvā dātā taponvitaḥ|
āhitāgniścaturvedaḥ sarvabhūtasukhāvahaḥ|| 77.11||
rājyārthe sa hato devairvikṛtyā mūḍhamānasaiḥ|
tasya duḥkhena tapyāmi śuṣyāmi ca mahāsurāḥ|| 77.12||
salilāduddhṛtaṃ grīṣme padmaṃ kusumitaṃ yathā|
teṣāṃ kartum ahaṃ daṇḍaṃ śakto 'asmyasuravidviṣām|| 77.13||
bhavatāṃ tatra bālānāṃ rakṣārthaṃ nodyato hyaham|
so 'ahaṃ daṇḍaṃ svayaṃ kartum ekākyasuravidviṣām|
gamiṣyāmi na saṃdeho mā bhīrbhavatu vo 'asurāḥ|| 77.14||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā dānavāste mudānvitāḥ|
parasparam udaikṣanta vrīḍayā parayānvitāḥ|| 77.15||
vipracittistadanujo bhrātaraṃ taṃ mahābalaḥ|
uvāca praṇataḥ samyagarthavanmadhuraṃ vacaḥ|| 77.16||
na saṃdeho mahāsattva tvayaikenāsuradviṣaḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 77.17||
yadi yuddhe na tiṣṭhanti māyāṃ kāṃcidvināśritāḥ|
abalāste na saṃdeho nikṛtyā balinastu te|| 77.18||
prasādayitvā śirasā yadbravīmi nibodha tat|
bālairapi hiraṇyākṣa sūpapattyā prasādhitam|| 77.19||
tadgrāhyam iti -- -- -- śāstravidbhiḥ samīritam|
hiraṇyakaśipuu rājā bhrātā no jyeṣṭha uttamaḥ|| 77.20||
so 'api śakto 'aham ityeva ekakkī daivatairhataḥ|
mahābalo 'api ca hariraśaktairhanyate balāt|| 77.21||
ākrandantaṃ vinā rājannato vijñāpayāmi te|
bhavatastu vayaṃ bālā na teṣām asureśvara|| 77.22||
śaktā vayaṃ suyuddhe na tān hantuṃ kulapāṃsanān|
tapoyogabalopetā māyābhiśca samanvitāḥ|| 77.23||
anusmaranto vairaṃ ca vayaṃ haṃsyāma daivatān|
yathā tava na nidrāsti hiraṇyakaśiporvadhāt|| 77.24||
tathāsmākaṃ mahārāja mā no bālān yathā cara|
yatra no yokṣyase rājan same vā viṣame 'api vā|| 77.25||
tariṣyāmo vayaṃ tadvai bālamatsyā ivārṇavam|
prahlādo 'ayaṃ sahabhrātā sasutaḥ sasuhṛjjanaḥ|| 77.26||
eka evāhvayet sarvān yathā siṃho mahādvipān|
balireṣa ca daityendra eka eva savāsavān|| 77.27||
surān sayamavitteśāñchaktaḥ sarvān prabādhitum|
ayaṃ bāṇaśca tatputro rājā bāhusahasradhṛk|| 77.28||
eka eva surān sarvān vināśayitum udyataḥ|
imau sundanisundau ca bhrātarau bāhuśālinau|| 77.29||
ubhāvekākinau yuddhe devān hantuṃ samudyatau|
ayaṃ mayaśca vikrāntaḥ sārakastāra eva ca|| 77.30||
anye ca dānavāḥ śūrāḥ śaktā devān prabādhitum|
ete 'apyatibalāḥ sarve balavanto vayaṃ sadā|| 77.31||
badhiṣyāmaḥ surān sarvān vyādhā iva mṛgān vane|
śūro 'ayam andhakaḥ śrīmān brahmadattavarastadā|| 77.32||
prasahya sarvāṃstān yuddhe neṣyate vai yamālayam|
evam enaṃ samāśritya pālitānena caiva hi|| 77.33||
kariṣyāmo mahadyuddhaṃ devatānāṃ bhayaṃkaram|
pūrvaṃ devā vayaṃ sarve paścāt te devatābhavan|| 77.34||
kathaṃ bibhīma teṣāṃ vai siṃhānāṃ śarabhā iva|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā andhakaḥ so 'asureśvaraḥ|| 77.35||
uvāca vacanaṃ tatra harṣayan dānaveśvarān|
mahābalā vayaṃ rājan balahīnāḥ surāstu te|| 77.36||
paśya tvaṃ daivatān sarvān hatān yamapurogamān|
adya taṃ rājahantāraṃ durātmānaṃ kulādhamam|| 77.37||
adya mātā ditisteṣāṃ duḥkham $I$-- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 77.38||
tiṣṭhadhvaṃ dānavāḥ sarve paryāpto 'ahaṃ durātmanām|
asmākaṃ rājahantR̥ṇāṃ mṛtyurasmi samāgataḥ|| 77.39||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca dānavān vyāsa jayepsuḥ suravidviṣām|| 77.40||
adya puṣyaṃ ca nakṣatram asmākaṃ balakāraṇam|
adyaiva daṃśitāḥ sarve drutaṃ niryātu dānavāḥ|| 77.41||
atha te dānavāḥ śīghraṃ vāhanāni mudā yutāḥ|
prāvārayanta saṃgrāme yogyāni ripubādhane|| 77.42||
śīghraṃ kurudhvaṃ sajjāni gacchāmo daivatān prati|
teṣāṃ sutumulaḥ śabdo vāhanānāṃ babhūva ha|| 77.43||
mandavātapreritasya kṣīrodasya svano yathā|
mamāśvastava siṃho 'ayaṃ mamāyaṃ gajayūthapaḥ|| 77.44||
ratho 'ayaṃ kasya sampanno yuddhopakaraṇairbhṛśam|
ehi niryāhi vegena muhūrtaṃ pratipālaya|| 77.45||
niryāntu sarva daityendrā yāsyāmaḥ pṛṣṭhato vayam|
āroha svaṃ rathaṃ vīra kiṃ rathena mamādya vai|
padātireva saṃgrāme haṃsyāmyadya suradviṣaḥ|| 77.46||
evaṃ teṣām abhūcchabdaḥ sumanojñaḥ suradviṣām|
vaṃśavīṇāsvanonmiśraḥ pralāpa iva yoṣitām|| 77.47||
atha śukrastadābhyetya bhṛgoḥ putro mahātapāḥ|
hiraṇyākṣam uvācedaṃ harṣayan dānaveśvaram|| 77.48||
mayā śāntiḥ kṛtā te 'adya rakṣā ca saha dānavaiḥ|
jahi sarvān surān yuddhe na tavāsti parājayaḥ|| 77.49||
ahaṃ tvā svena tapasā sahabhṛtyaṃ sabāndhavam|
dhārayiṣyāmi yudhyantaṃ lokān yajña ivāparaḥ|| 77.50||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ pradakṣiṇaṃ kṛtvā śukraṃ mūrdhnā praṇamya ca|
bhārgavaṃ purataḥ kṛtvā nirjagāma sa mandirāt|| 77.51||
tato bheryaśca śaṅkhāśca praṇavānakagomukhāḥ|
sāḍastamā diṇḍimāśca bhāṇḍāśca paṭahaiḥ saha|| 77.52||
jharjharyo dardurāścaiva sunavā mardalāstathā|
kaṭaṃkaṭāḥ pepukāśca tathā caivaikapuṣkalāḥ|| 77.53||
pañcākṣāḥ saridhīkāśca mukundā murajāstathā|
labhakā jalamattāśca avādyanta sahasraśaḥ|| 77.54||
gāyanaiścaiva gāyadbhiḥ stuvadbhiḥ sūtamāgadhaiḥ|
divyābhiḥ kulavṛddhābhiḥ strībhiśca kṛtamaṅgalāḥ|| 77.55||
dvāryapaśyan rathaṃ kḷptaṃ yathā devamayaṃ haraḥ|
śatanalvapramāṇāṅkaṃ divyaṃ jāmbūnadaṃ dṛḍham|| 77.56||
asaṅgaturagaiḥ śvetaistrisāhasrairmanojavaiḥ|
amaraiḥ kāmagairdivyaiḥ śramaduḥkhavivarjitaiḥ|| 77.57||
yantā rathasya tasyāsīnmakaro nāma viśrutaḥ|
putro garutmano vyāsa khagaḥ kāmagamaḥ śubhaḥ|| 77.58||
tam asau rājaśabdena āśīrbhiścābhipūjitaḥ|
āruroha rathaṃ rājā ekacakraṃ yathā raviḥ|| 77.59||
kavacī baddhatūṇīraḥ śarī khaḍgī śarāsanī|
baddhagodhāṅgulitraśca kaṇṭhatrāṇakṛtastathā|| 77.60||
dhvajena mahatā caiva chatreṇa ca vibhūṣitaḥ|
bahvībhirvaijayantībhiḥ sabalāka ivāmbudaḥ|| 77.61||
tasya chatraṃ tadā bhāti kirīṭopari saṃsthitam|
āviṣkṛtapayodābhaḥ paurṇamāsyāṃ yathā śaśī|| 77.62||
khaṭvāṅgastasya cābhāti dhvajo divam ivākraman|
trailokyasyopaghātārthaṃ keturdīpta ivoditaḥ|| 77.63||
tādṛgeva ratho hi āsīt sutasya sumahātmanaḥ|
andhakasya tadā vyāsa mahājaladanisvanaḥ|| 77.64||
atha yāhīti tenokto rathayantā suradviṣaḥ|
trisāhasrān hayāgryāṃstu yān rathe pratyacūcudat|| 77.65||
pracoditāstam ūḍhuste javanā vātaraṃhasaḥ|
hayāḥ kāmagamāḥ sapta raveriva mahāratham|| 77.66||
tasyāgratastadā śukro rathenāmbudanādinā|
udgacchata iva vyomni tasyaivābhūdyathā budhaḥ|| 77.67||
dakṣiṇe tasya pārśve ca abhūdandhakadānavaḥ|
dakṣiṇāyanam āsādya yathā lokasya bhāskaraḥ|| 77.68||
dvitīyaṃ pārśvam āśritya vipracittirabhūt sthitaḥ|
bhāratasyeva varṣasya himavān parvatottamaḥ|| 77.69||
pṛṣṭhataścāgrataścaiva yathāprīti yayustadā|
apare dānavāḥ śūrāḥ śaśāṅkasya yathā grahāḥ|| 77.70||
tat sainyaṃ pracaladbhāti vrajatāṃ munisattama|
savidyutstanayitunūnām ambhodānām ivātyaye|| 77.71||
hayahreṣitaśabdaṃ ca mattadviradabṛṃhitam|
valgitāsphoṭitotkruṣṭaṃ siṃhanādoddhataṃ yayau|| 77.72||
taddhi tūryaravasiṃhanāditairaśvaheṣitagajograbṛṃhitaiḥ|
bāhuśabdakucitāvanāditairyāti dānavabalaṃ bhayāvaham|| 77.73||
iti skandapurāṇe
hiraṇyākṣaniryāṇaṃ nāma
saptasaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 77.77||

aṣṭasaptatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
kṛṣṇadvaipāyana uvāca|
bhagavan ditiputreṣu prayāteṣvamarāvatīm|
amarāḥ kim akurvaṃsta etadicchāmi veditum|| 78.1||
katham antarhitaṃ teṣāṃ ko mantraśceṣṭitaṃ ca kim|
uttaraṃ kiṃ ca devāste pratyapadyanta yatnataḥ|| 78.2||
dhārmikāśca vadānyāśca vidvāṃsaśchinnasaṃśayāḥ|
iṣṭāḥ sarvasya lokasya kim akurvata devatāḥ|| 78.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vyāsa yathā devā uttaraṃ pratipedire|
asurāṇāṃ ca yadyuktaṃ pratyakurvata daṃśitāḥ|| 78.4||
udyukteṣveva daityeṣu devānāṃ bhayasūcakāḥ|
saṃjajñire 'amarāvatyām utpātā dāruṇā bhṛśam|| 78.5||
piśitāśāḥ khagāstatra bhramantyupari sarvataḥ|
mamlurmālyāni devānāṃ gandhaścaivāśubhaṃ vavau|| 78.6||
hayādayo na heṣante vimanāśca gajo 'abhavat|
anabhraṃ bhayadaṃ sarvam apatadrudhiraṃ bahu|| 78.7||
āyudhāni ca dīpyante sadhūmaṃ śaktinandana|
kabandhāśca tathāditye yuddhaṃ cātra pradṛśyate|| 78.8||
dvayoḥ puruṣayorvyāsa hāhākāraśca sarvaśaḥ|
devānām aratiṃ caiva cittaṃ vāpi samaśnute|| 78.9||
sphuranti vāmanetrāṇi jṛmbhikā copajāyate|
vayāṃsi ca vikūjanti bhayadānyapare yathā|
agniśca dīpyate tatra saśabdo rūkṣa eva ca|| 78.10||
etāṃścānyāṃśca vividhānutpātān bhayasūcakān|
dṛṣṭvā prāha guruṃ śakro bṛhaspatim idaṃ vacaḥ|| 78.11||
bhagavan kim idaṃ ghoraṃ bhayaṃ naḥ samupasthitam|
yadime sūcayantyugrā utpātā naḥ sudāruṇāḥ|| 78.12||
neme niṣkāraṇaṃ manye na cālpyalpaṃ hi taddhi naḥ|
yadime sūcayantyugrāḥ kalpānta iva dāruṇāḥ|| 78.13||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā devācāryo bṛhaspatiḥ|
nirīkṣya buddhyā saṃcintya provācedaṃ tato vacaḥ|| 78.14||
yadbhavān āha tat tathyaṃ neme niṣkāraṇaṃ tathā|
nimittam atra sumahadbhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|| 78.15||
nimittam ādidaityendro hiraṇyakaśipuḥ purā|
sa hato narasiṃhena prāptaṃ rājyaṃ ca naḥ punaḥ|| 78.16||
adya varṣasahasrāṇi dvādaśaiva sunirvṛtaiḥ|
yuṣmābhirakhilā lokā bhujyante sumahātmabhiḥ|| 78.17||
daityādhipā nirutsāhā dānavaiḥ saha śerate|
pātāle danuputrāśca duḥkhaśokasamāhatāḥ|| 78.18||
hiraṇyākṣastu daityednro hiraṇyakaśiporvaraḥ|
sa nūnaṃ bhrāturanvicchan hatasya pratikāritām|| 78.19||
sarvairabhyeti daityendrairdānavaiśca samāvṛtaḥ|
saputrapautro daityendro mahābalaparākramaḥ|| 78.20||
andhakaścāsya putro 'api brahmaṇā hyamaraḥ kṛtaḥ|
na sa śakyo yuvā hantuṃ tato vo bhayam utthitam|| 78.21||
tadbhavantaḥ susaṃnaddhāḥ sarve yuddhāya daṃśitāḥ|
pratīkṣadhvaṃ mahāsattvā yāvadautpātikaṃ sthitam|| 78.22||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā śakraḥ sarvāṃstadā surān|
uvāca sajjībhavata yuddhāya kṛtaniścayāḥ|| 78.23||
bhayaṃ mahadidaṃ prāptaṃ mā tiṣṭhata nirudyamāḥ|
mā naḥ samprāpya daityendrā hanyurmattānivāmarāḥ|| 78.24||
atha vāyustadābhyetya śakraṃ sarvāsurāntakam|
uvāca prāñjalirbhūtvā devānām eva saṃsadi|| 78.25||
eṣa daityo hiraṇyākṣaḥ sarvāsurasamāvṛtaḥ|
āyāti devatā hantuṃ bhrāturvadham anusmaran|| 78.26||
tadbhavān daṃśitaḥ samyak sahāsmābhirmahābalaḥ|
jayāyottiṣṭha devendra vināśāya suradviṣām|| 78.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān vyāsa mahātmā devarāṭ svayam|
abhedyaṃ kavacaṃ divyaṃ jāmbūnadavibhūṣitam|| 78.28||
dattaṃ mantreṇa vidhivat putreṇāṅgirasaḥ svayam|
ābabaddhātmanā śakro meghadundubhinisvanaḥ|| 78.29||
sa tena kavacena sma bhāti śakraḥ pratāpavān|
savidyudulkairambhodairbaddho merurivācalaḥ|| 78.30||
tato godhāṅgulitrāṇi talatraṃ caiva bhāsuram|
ābabaddha svayaṃ mantraistasya devo bṛhaspatiḥ|| 78.31||
iṣudhīnakṣayāṃścaiva khaṅgaṃ caivāmṛtodbhavam|
ābabaddhāsya mantreṇa yadajaryaṃ śarādibhiḥ|| 78.32||
tato 'asmai saśaraṃ cāpaṃ pañcavajraṃ sudāruṇam|
mantrābhimantritaṃ samyak pradadau jayavarddhanam|| 78.33||
maṅgalāni tastastasya darśayāmāsa vīryavān|
ghaṭaṃ ca pūrṇam astraṃ ca airāvatam athāpi ca|| 78.34||
kalpitaṃ bahubhirdivyairācāryaiḥ kalpavāsibhiḥ|
arcitaṃ dhūpitaṃ caiva dhūpitaṃ krodhadarpaṇaiḥ|| 78.35||
tatastaṃ sa tadā deva āruroha mataṅgajam|
bhadralakṣaṇasampannaṃ caturdantaṃ kṣaran madam|| 78.36||
āruḍhaḥ sa tadā bhāti airāvatagakaṃ vibhuḥ|
udayācalamaulistha udyanniva divākaraḥ|| 78.37||
pāṇḍareṇātapatreṇa surarāṭ sambabhau tadā|
śvetaparvatarājo 'asau śaśineva mahāmune|| 78.38||
cāmarāvījitaṃ bhāti tasya vaktram atiprabham|
haṃsasaṃvījitaṃ phullaṃ śaradīva mahotpalam|| 78.39||
tasya pārśve jayantaśca putraḥ śakrasya dhārmikaḥ|
kārtikeya ivābhāti rudrasya dayitaḥ sutaḥ|| 78.40||
tato yamaśca puṇḍreṇa mahiṣeṇa mahābalaḥ|
kāladaṇḍaṃ puraskṛtya koṭībhirdaśabhirvṛtaḥ|| 78.41||
nirjagāma kuberaśca rākṣasairbahubhirvṛtaḥ|
yakṣaiḥ puṇyajanaiścāpi tathānyairdevatairapi|| 78.42||
teṣāṃ dvādaśa koṭyastāḥ sahasrāṇi ca viṃśatiḥ|
śatāni ca tathāśītistathaivāṣṭādhikā punaḥ|| 78.43||
varuṇo niryayau devaḥ putrāṇāṃ daśabhiḥ śataiḥ|
yādobhiste vṛtāḥ sarve koṭyastāścaikaviṃśatiḥ|| 78.44||
analaśca tato devaḥ koṭībhirdaśabhirvṛtaḥ|
niryayau saha putreṇa sasuhṛdvargabāndhavaḥ|| 78.45||
tato vāyurmahātejāḥ sarvavyāpī mahājavaḥ|
akṣauhiṇībhirdaśabhirnirjagāma mahābalaḥ|| 78.46||
ādityā niryayuḥ sarve dvādaśākṣauhiṇīvṛtāḥ|
ekaikaśaśca te vyāsa sarve divyāstrayodhinaḥ|| 78.47||
tathā rudrāśca nirjagmurmahāmāyāmahābalāḥ|
ekaikaśastadā sarve ṣoḍaśākṣauhiṇīvṛtāḥ|| 78.48||
vasavo daśabhiścaiva aṣṭābhiścāśvināvubhau|
tathaivāṅgiraso devāḥ sarve te 'akṣauhiṇīvṛtāḥ|| 78.49||
yāmā dāmāśca sādhyāśca lekhā ye ca mahābalāḥ|
te 'api koṭīśataiḥ sarve daśabhiḥ saha saṃgatāḥ|| 78.50||
abhūvan viṃśatiḥ koṭyo gandharvāṇāṃ mahātmanām|
pannagānāṃ catuḥṣaṣṭiḥ khagānāṃ caiva viṃśatiḥ|| 78.51||
piśācānāṃ ca koṭyastāḥ pañcāśat tatra saṃgatāḥ|
rājñāṃ sa-- -- -- -- -- -- -- --nāṃ mahātmanām|| 78.52||
etaddevabalaṃ sarvam abhūt tatrābhisaṃgatam|
dṛṣṭvā tadbahvaparyantaṃ devānāṃ balam uttamam|| 78.53||
uvāca jīvaṃjīvānāṃ rājā paramadharmavit|
bhagavan kriyatāṃ vyūho yasmāt teṣāṃ durātmanām|| 78.54||
adhṛṣyaścāprameyaśca yanna vetti ca bhārgavaḥ|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bṛhadbuddhirbṛhaspatiḥ|| 78.55||
uvāca devatādhyakṣaṃ śakraṃ daivatasannidhau|
na tadasti maheṣvāsa mayi yadbhārgavo mahān|| 78.56||
na vetti yasya vā bhedaṃ na kuryāt pākaśāsana|
uśanāḥ sa tu yadvetti mahāyogī mahāyaśāḥ|| 78.57||
na caiva tadahaṃ vedmi matto varataro hi saḥ|
sa tu tīkṣṇatayā caiva mānāccaiva śacīpate|| 78.58||
pramādaṃ kurute teṣu na ca sarvatra labhyate|
ahaṃ ca vijñabhāvena mārdavena pareṇa ca|| 78.59||
apramattaśca sarvatra tava sainyaiśca rakṣitaḥ|
buddhyā tam atiricyāmi vibudheśvara nityaśaḥ|| 78.60||
tasmāt te 'ahaṃ kariṣyāmi vyūhaṃ śyenam atiprabham|
yena tān dānavān saṃkhye kaṃcit kālaṃ vijeṣyatha|| 78.61||
tataḥ sa bhagavāñjīvaścakre vyūham atiprabham|
śyenaṃ nāma mahāyogī devānāṃ hitam ādadhat|| 78.62||
grīvāyāṃ tasya saṃcakre vitteśaṃ varuṇaṃ tathā|
analaṃ caiva vāyuṃ ca jayantaṃ caiva śakrajam|| 78.63||
śiraścūḍāṃ yamaṃ tasya mṛtyuṃ kālaṃ ca tāvubhau|
vaktraṃ tasyākarojjīvaścandrasūryau ca cakṣuṣī|| 78.64||
ekaṃ pakṣaṃ cakārāsya rudrān sarvān sa vai dvijaḥ|
dvitīyaṃ pakṣam ādityān madhyaṃ tasya purandaram|| 78.65||
pādau ca vasavastasya aśvinau ca mahātalau|
gandharvāḥ pannagāścaiva nakhāṃstasya samāśritāḥ|| 78.66||
pakṣiṇaśca mahāsattvāḥ piśācāśca mahābalāḥ|
pucchaṃ tasyākarot sarpān devānanyāṃstadodaram|| 78.67||
rājānastasya pādasthāstale bhūtān nyaveśayat|
mahābalān mahotsāhān sarvān devān sabhāsadaḥ|| 78.68||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa kṛtvā taṃ khagavyūhaṃ mantreṇaivābhimantrya ca|
uvāca devarājaṃ taṃ bṛhaspatiridaṃ vacaḥ|| 78.69||
kalpito 'ayaṃ mayā vyūhaḥ kṛtvā rākṣasapārthivam (?)|
ataḥ paraṃ vidhānasya karma nāsmāsu vidyate|| 78.70||
jaya śatrūn raṇe śakra devatairabhirakṣitaḥ|
mayā cātharvaṇairmantraistapasāṃ ca balena ca|| 78.71||
kuru karma yathāśakti hyamaro hyasi pārthiva|
devāścāpyamarāḥ sarve yudhyantu surapārthiva|| 78.72||
bhāgyān no jaya lābhāya nānyatra surapuṃgava|
jahi śatrūn mahābāho mā bhīrbhavatu te raṇe|| 78.73||
tataḥ śaṅkhāśca bheryaśca paṭahā ḍiṇḍimāstathā|
āḍambarāśca nambhāśca (?)kṛkavā goviṣāṇakāḥ|| 78.74||
mardalāḥ pepukāścitrā nedustūryāṇi sarvaśaḥ|
tena śabdena yodhānāṃ yuddhaharṣo mahānabhūt|
siṃhanādānakurvaṃste vāditāsphoṭitāni ca||| 78.75||
devāstataḥ śaṅkhamṛdaṅgavādyairamoghasarvāyudhadīptahastāḥ|
nirjagmurindrādisurapradhānā jayaiṣiṇaḥ śatruvadhepsavaśca|| 78.76||
iti skandapurāṇe
vyyuharacano nāma
aṣṭasaptatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 78.78||

ekonāśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vyūḍhe surāṇāṃ sainye 'atha sthite yuddhāya daṃśite|
dānavānāṃ balaṃ ghoraṃ samadṛśyata bhīṣaṇam|| 79.1||
taddānavabalaṃ dṛṣṭvā devāḥ sarve savāsavāḥ|
siṃhanādānakurvaṃste vāditraravamiśritān|| 79.2||
sa nādaḥ sumahān vyāsa sāgarasyeva mathyataḥ|
āpūrayajjagat sarvaṃ yugāntāmbudanisvanaḥ|| 79.3||
tato dānavaśārdūlāḥ sarve dṛṣṭvā surottamān|
vyūhya sainyaṃ sthitān samyagvīkṣāṃcakruḥ parasparam|| 79.4||
tān vīkṣamāṇān saṃdṛśya sthito dānavayūthapān|
uvāca bhārgavaṃ vyāsa hiraṇyanayanaḥ svayam|| 79.5||
ete vyūham imaṃ kṛtvā devāstiṣṭhantyabhītavat|
manyante dānavān yuddhe vayaṃ jeṣyāma sarvaśaḥ|| 79.6||
sa bhavān yuktam asyaiva devavyūhasya bhedakam|
kuru māyāprativyūham asmākam api mā ciram|| 79.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam astviti samprocya hyardhacandraṃ cakāra saḥ|
khagasya tasya yacchettuṃ śiraḥ kāyādiyeṣa ca|| 79.8||
cakāra tasya śṛṅge tu prahlādāndhakadānavau|
dhārān nivātakavacān paulomān kālakāsutān|| 79.9||
virocanaṃ baliṃ caiva vipracittiṃ sahānujaiḥ|
prahlādabhrātaraṃ caiva sasuhṛdvargabāndhavān || 79.10||
pṛṣṭhaṃ cakre mahāyogī madhyaṃ rājānam eva ca|
uvāca cainaṃ viśrabdho bhārgavaḥ śatrutāpanaḥ|| 79.11||
hiraṇyākṣam idaṃ yuktaṃ kāle pathyaṃ ca sarvaśaḥ|
daivatavyūhabhettāyaṃ mahāvyūho hi vaḥ kṛtaḥ|| 79.12||
yuktaṃ kuruta bhadraṃ vo mayānuparipālitāḥ|
parasparaṃ ca rakṣantaḥ sarve citrāstrayodhinaḥ|
mahāmāyāḥ surāḥ sarve yathā naivābhimanyata|| 79.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ śaṅkhāśca bheryaśca paṇavānakagomukhāḥ|
āḍambarā ḍiṇḍimāśca paṭahāśca mahāsvanāḥ|| 79.14||
nānāvidhāni cānyāni prāvādyanta sahasraśaḥ|
devānāṃ dānavānāṃ ca madasattvapradāni vai|| 79.15||
tataḥ pramathnatetyuktā dānavā dānaveśvaraiḥ|
mamardurdevatānīkaṃ prahatāḥ sarvaśastathā|| 79.16||
devāste 'api ca saṃyattāstapoyogabalānvitāḥ|
dānavān vividhaiḥ śastrairabhijaghnuḥ kṛtāgasaḥ|| 79.17||
asīnāṃ pātyamānānāṃ śirasāṃ hastinām api|
āsīcchabdo mahāghoro vaṃśānām iva pāṭyatām|| 79.18||
vikṛṣyatāṃ ca dhanuṣāṃ bāṇānāṃ ca vimucyatām|
āsīt tatra mahāñchabdo girīṇām iva bhidyatām|| 79.19||
gacchadbhirbhindipālaiśca śaktibhistomaraistathā|
ākāśam abhavat sarvaṃ ^khadyotairiva saṃvṛtam|| 79.20||
śirobhiścaraṇaiścaiva bāhubhiśca nipātitaiḥ|
kṣaṇena yuddhabhūmiḥ sā viṣamā samapadyata|| 79.21||
dantibhiḥ parvatākārairhayavaryairathottamaiḥ|
kabandhaiścābhinṛtyadbhirdurnirīkṣyam abhūdraṇe|| 79.22||
ātapatraiśca hāraiśca kavacaistalacairapi (?)|
niṣkasūtraiḥ sumukuṭaiḥ keyūraiḥ kuṇḍalairapi|| 79.23||
kaṇṭhatrāṇairvicitraiśca dukūlairmaṇibhiśca ha|
kuthābhiśca vicitrābhirbhujaiḥ sābharaṇairapi|| 79.24||
muśalaiḥ śūladaṇḍaiśca ghaṇṭābhiścāṅkuśairapi|
vibhāti bhūtalaṃ tatra jyotirbhirdyaurivāvṛtam|| 79.25||
kruddhaḥ keśeṣu saṃgṛhya viratho 'api mahārathaḥ|
rathinaṃ ratham āplutya nijaghāna balādbalī|| 79.26||
tatra cānyo gaje cāśurabhihatya mahābhujaḥ|
rathaṃ cikṣepa ca vṛtaiḥ kuśamuṣṭim ivādhvare|| 79.27|| (?)
kṣipto gajāt samutpatya -- nasaṃ -- -- -- ya --|
śarairāśīviṣākārairanayadyamasādanam|| 79.28||
hatam apyeṣa turagaḥ sādinaṃ patitaṃ kṣitau|
upāste pādataḥ suptaṃ guruṃ śiṣyo yathātmavān|| 79.29||
sasūte nihate yodhe ratham ete hayottamāḥ|
vahanti puruṣāḥ kṣīvā jñānavanta ivāgamān|| 79.30||
ayam anyaḥ subaddho 'api daityena surapuṃgavaḥ|
bāhubhyāṃ veṣṭayitvā taṃ prayayau devatāntikam|| 79.31|| (?)
ayam ādhāvataḥ paśya gajasya bhujam ācchinat|
sa tenaiva gajenorvyāṃ papāta viniṣūditaḥ|| 79.32||
ayam anyena saṃyukto 'anyenāgatya ghātinaḥ|
sa cāpyanyena devena so 'apyanyena punarhataḥ|| 79.33||
ete padātayaścānye bahavaḥ saṃhatā bhṛśam|
rathinaṃ mohayitvā tu jaghnurenam abhītavat|| 79.34||
evam ākāśagāḥ siddhā ṛṣayaścāraṇāstathā|
śodhayanti ramante ca smayanti ca japanti ca|| 79.35||
harantyapsarasaścaiva yodhāṃstatra raṇe hatān|
piśācāścāpi modante nṛtyanti ca nikumbhilāḥ|| 79.36||
tat pravāditagāndharvaṃ chinnabhinnavidāritam|
yuddhagāndharvam abhavadbhīrūṇāṃ bhayavarddhanam|| 79.37||
anyonyaghātakṣatasarvadehāḥ surāsurā vairam anusmarantaḥ|
jaghnustadā rākṣasatulyarūpāḥ svārājyahetorjayam īpsamānāḥ|| 79.38||
iti skandapurāṇe
devāsurasaṃgrāmanāmaikonāśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 79.79||

aśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasmin mahati yuddhe tu vartamāne mahābhaye|
dānavān vai tadā devāḥ samantān paryavārayan|| 80.1||
mṛtyuḥ kālo yamaścaiva kṛtāntaḥ kalahastathā|
nikṛtirvyādhayaścaiva vairaṃ krodhaśca vīryavān|| 80.2||
narakāścaiva te sarve yamadūtāśca sarvaśaḥ|
pretāśca pitaraścaiva catvāro ye gaṇāstviti|| 80.3||
vāmanaścaiva yo devāḥ kiṃkarāśca mahābalāḥ|
ete sarve tadāviśya saṃjaghnurdānavaṃ balam|| 80.4||
yamadūtairvibhinnāṅgā bhagnavakṣatrikorasaḥ|
niṣṭananti kṣitau daityā nirayeṣviva pāpinaḥ|| 80.5||
asicarmaviniṣpiṣṭā mṛtyupāśovapāśitāḥ|
kṛtāntavaśagāḥ sarve sambhajyanti diteḥ sutāḥ|| 80.6||
te hanyamānā daityendrā mṛtyunā ca yamena ca|
trātāram alabhanto vai tatra tatraiva babhramuḥ|| 80.7||
tathā tāṃstatra tatraiva bhramanto jaghnurarditāḥ|
tato hāhākṛtaḥ śabdo dānavānāṃ bale 'abhavat|| 80.8||
sādhu sādhviti devānāṃ yamaṃ pūjayatām abhūt|
atha prahlādatanayo virocana iti śrutaḥ|| 80.9||
sa gajena tato 'abhyetya devānāṃ balam ārdayat|
saha tena mahāmāyo gajena samadhāvata|| 80.10||
yamaṃ pradakṣiṇaṃ kṛtvā droṇamegha ivāparaḥ|
sa śarairbahubhistīkṣṇairakuṇṭhāgrairayomayaiḥ|| 80.11||
varuṇaṃ ca dhaneśaṃ ca vāyuṃ caivābhyavarṣata|
sa saṃchādya tadā bhāsaṃ bhāskarasya śitaiḥ karaiḥ|
avākirat tadā devān saṃvarttaka ivāmbudaḥ|| 80.12||
te śarārcitasarvāṅgā vadhyamānāḥ punaḥ punaḥ|
kṣaṇena samapadyanta devāḥ sarve vicetasaḥ|| 80.13||
yāntam āyāntam aprāptaṃ prāptaṃ dūrastham eva ca|
yaṃ yato vīkṣate daityastaṃ tato 'abhijaghāna saḥ|| 80.14||
nityāyatadhanurdaityaḥ pariveṣīva bhāskaraḥ|
durnirīkṣyaḥ samabhavadyugāntāgnirivotthitaḥ|| 80.15||
athaivam asyato vyāsa varuṇaḥ kārmukaṃ tadā|
ciccheda sumahaddhīmāṃstarjayan dānaveśvaram|| 80.16||
vāyustīkṣṇaśaraistasya kavacaṃ sarvato 'aharat|
dhaneśo 'aśanighātena gajam asya nyasūdayat|| 80.17||
taṃ tathā nikṛtaṃ dṛṣṭvā balirbāṇaśca tāvubhau|
prahlādo bhrātṛbhiḥ sārdhaṃ lokapālānupādravan|| 80.18||
teṣām āpatatām eva lokapālā mahābalāḥ|
śarairāśīviṣākāraiścakrarakṣānapothayan|| 80.19||
vāyurbāṇasya viśikhaiḥ kārmukāṇi vikarṣataḥ|
ciccheda yugapadvyāsa tadadbhutam ivābhavat|| 80.20||
vicchinnadhanvā sa kruddhastomarāṇi tadāsṛjat|
cikṣepa tāni vegena vāyuranyāṃ diśaṃ punaḥ|| 80.21||
hayāṃśca punarevāsya śaraiḥ sannataparvabhiḥ|
sasūtān param āyasto hyanayadyamasādanam|| 80.22||
sa rathādbalijaḥ krodhādavaplutya mahābalaḥ|
gadāṃ gṛhītvā vegena śvasanaṃ samupādravat|| 80.23||
tasyāpatata evāśu sagadasyānilastathā|
śarairāśīviṣākārairgadāṃ tāṃ samakṛntata|| 80.24||
sa nikṛttagadaścāpi bāṇaḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|
pragṛhya tu gadām anyāṃ cikṣepa ca jahāsa ca|| 80.25||
tām āpatantīṃ vegena gadāṃ bāṇasya khecarīm|
ākṣipya vāyurvyadhamadanyāṃ diśam adīnavat|| 80.26||
virathaṃ tam athālakṣya vāyunā ca bhṛśārditam|
putraṃ balirdrutaṃ vyāsa svarathe samapādayat|| 80.27||
tāvekarathasaṃyuktau babhaturdānaveśvarau|
sūryācandramasau yadvat pūrṇamāsyāṃ samāgatau|| 80.28||
atha teṣāṃ ca teṣāṃ ca tadyuddham abhavat tadā|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
tān niruddhānathājñāya lokapālairmahābalaiḥ|| 80.29||
nivātakavacāḥ sarve kālakeyāśca daṃśitāḥ|
paulomāḥ saiṃhikeyāśca śambaraḥ kālaśambaraḥ|| 80.30||
andhakaśca mahādaityo hiraṇyākṣaśca viśrutaḥ|
sarve vyūham amuñcanto dānavā yuddhalālasāḥ|| 80.31||
cakrurvegaṃ mahāvegāḥ sameghā iva sānavaḥ|
tān āpatata evātha yamo daṇḍena vīryavān|| 80.32||
avārayata te tasthuścitrapaṭṭa ivārpitāḥ|
tān yamasya bhayāddaityān dṛṣṭvā sarvānavasthitān|| 80.33||
andhako yamam abhyetya tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti cābravīt|
mahatā sa rathenaitya dhanurvisphālya cāsakṛt|| 80.34||
yamaṃ lalāṭe daśabhirbāṇairvivyādha vīryavān|
pañcabhirmahiṣaṃ cāsya ṣaḍbhiḥ kālaṃ tathāgrataḥ|| 80.35||
mṛtyuṃ ca daśabhiścaiva kṛtāntaṃ caiva saptabhiḥ|
bhrāmayan sa punaścāpam indrāyudhasamaprabham|| 80.36||
nanādāmbudavaccaiva punarvivyādha daivatam|
hiraṇyākṣasuto jyeṣṭho hyandhako 'ahaṃ mahābalaḥ|| 80.37||
brahmaṇā ca varo datto mahyam ityavaghoṣayat|
tasyaivaṃ vadatastūrṇaṃ sūryaputraḥ pratāpavān|| 80.38||
rathaṃ ciccheda saṃkruddho daṇḍena vinipātayan|
sakārmuke rathe tatra mathite hyandhakastadā|| 80.39||
gadām udyamya vegena pretādhipam athādravat|
tasya tāṃ daṇḍaghātena gadāṃ so 'apyavacūrṇayat|| 80.40||
śirasyenaṃ punaḥ kruddho daṇḍena samatāḍayat|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 80.41||
jitendriyo muniryadvat spṛṣṭo viṣayagocaraiḥ|| (?)
athāpratihataṃ daṇḍam andhakena parāhatam|| 80.42||
puraḥ pratihataṃ dṛṣṭvā jahasurdānaveśvarāḥ|
siṃhanādān savāditrān bāhuśabdāṃśca susvarān|| 80.43||
cakruḥ sādhvandhaketyevaṃ cakruśuśca muhurmuhuḥ|
andhako 'api tadābhyetya nardamāno yathārṇavaḥ|| 80.44||
talenāhatya mahiṣādyamaṃ bhūmau nyapātayat|
tato hāhākṛtaṃ devairgṛhṇa gṛhṇeti dānavaiḥ|| 80.45||
vyūhabhaṅgaśca devānām abhavacchaktinandana|
atha mṛtyuśca kālaśca kṛtāntaśceti te trayaḥ|| 80.46||
andhakaṃ bahubhiḥ pāśairbabandhuḥ krodhamūrcchitāḥ|
pāśāṃścaiva sa daityendro vicchidya sumahābalaḥ|
bāhupāśena balavān kṛtāntam avabadhnata|| 80.47||
sa baddho bāhupāśena kṛtāntaḥ krodhamūrcchitaḥ|
utkṣipyāndhakam uddhūto nināya balavān balāt|| 80.48||
taṃ nīyamānaṃ samprekṣya hiraṇāykṣaḥ sutaṃ svakam|
jaghāna sāyakaistīkṣṇaiḥ kṛtāntaṃ subhṛśaṃ dṛḍham|| 80.49||
tasya gātrāṇi sarvāṇi sandhīṃścaiva mahābalaḥ|
vivyādha niśitairbāṇaiḥ sa viṣṭabdho vyatiṣṭhata|| 80.50||
taṃ bāṇairvivṛtaṃ dṛṣṭvā devāḥ sarve savāsavāḥ|
rakṣantaḥ samapadyanta bhīmodyatakarāyudhāḥ|| 80.51||
atha kikharamṛdaṅgaveṇuvīṇāpaṇavasughoṣakaḍiṇḍimānakānām|
asurasurabale mahāṃstadānīṃ samabhavadugrataraḥ sa tūryanādaḥ|| 80.52||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe 'aśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 80.80||

ekāśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
hiraṇyākṣastadāyāntaṃ dṛṣṭvā devendram agrataḥ|
uvāca rathayantāram indraṃ prati nayasva mām|| 81.1||
sa tena coditastasya codayānastadā hayān|
anayattaṃ surendrāya hutaṃ bhāgaṃ yathānalaḥ|| 81.2||
sa gajaskandhagaṃ devaṃ sahasrākṣaṃ sureśvaram|
śarapāte tadā sthitvā provācāsurapuṅgavaḥ|| 81.3||
śakra yat te balaṃ kiṃcit tadvidarśaya mā ciram|
pūrvadevā vayaṃ caiva trailokyaṃ cākhilaṃ hi naḥ|| 81.4||
jyeṣṭhakramāgataṃ kṛtvā nyāyena ca surottama|
te yūyaṃ nyāyam utsṛjya hatvā me bhrātaraṃ punaḥ|| 81.5||
viśrambheṇa śaṭā bhūtvā paścāddevatvam āgatāḥ|
ime vayaṃ pūrvadevā navā yūyaṃ ca devatāḥ|| 81.6||
yudhyatāṃ vedmi sarveṣāṃ jīvitāni harāmyaham|
sahānugaistvām ihādya hatvā kṛtvā baliṃ tathā|| 81.7||
bhaviṣyāmyanṛṇo bhrāturyastvayā māyayā hataḥ|
sa evam uktvā balavaddhanurākṛṣya vīryavān|
lalāṭe pañcabhirvyāsa vivyādha niśitaiḥ śaraiḥ|| 81.8||
sa viddhastena devānāṃ lalāṭe pañcabhiḥ śaraiḥ|
rājā babhau yathā meruḥ sūryapādaiḥ samāvṛtaḥ|| 81.9||
atha tasya tadā śakraḥ punaśa caṅkramato dhanuḥ|
ciccheda vajram ādāya punaścainam atāḍayat|| 81.10||
sa tena suprahāreṇa diśo dīptā hyapaśyataḥ|
anyacca dhanurādāya punareva vyakarṣata|| 81.11||
tadapyasyācchinadrājā tathānyadbhūya eva ca|
atha śaktiṃ samādāya cikṣepa ruṣitastadā|| 81.12||
tām āpatantīṃ dīptāsyām ugrāṃ mṛtyoriva svasām|
vajreṇa rājā ciccheda tadadbhutam ivābhavat|| 81.13||
gadām anyāṃ samudyamya hiraṇyākṣastadā śubhām|
abhidudrāva vegena kruddhaḥ siṃha iva dvipam|| 81.14||
tasyāpatata evāśu gadāṃ hemapariṣkṛtām|
ciccheda bahudhā rājā dharmārthāviva nāstikaḥ|| 81.15||
athainaṃ vipracittiśca śinirvāṣkalireva ca|
mayaśca sambaraścaiva asilomā ca dānavaḥ|| 81.16||
tāraśca kārakaścaiva tathendradamanaḥ sa ca|
kālanemiśca ṣaṇḍaśca vipākaḥ pāka eva ca|| 81.17||
ilvalo namuciścaiva vātāpī kālamuñjikaḥ|
ete sarve mahāmāyā devendram abhidudruvuḥ|| 81.18||
tān āpatata evātha rudrādityāḥ pramanyavaḥ|
rurudhurvijane yadvadgajān siṃhāḥ samūrjitāḥ|| 81.19||
teṣāṃ teṣāṃ ca saṃgrāmaḥ sughoraḥ samapadyata|
araṇye 'anyonyasampātān mattānāṃ dantinām iva|| 81.20||
tatrāṃśo nāma ādityo rathenāmbudanādinā|
āyamya kārmukaṃ vyāsa dānavān samupādravat|| 81.21||
sa vipracittiṃ daśabhiḥ śiniṃ pañcabhireva ca|
tribhiśca vāṣkaliṃ saṃkhye mayaṃ pañcabhireva ca|| 81.22||
saṃvaraṃ caiva viṃśatyā asilomānam eva ca|
tāraṃ ca tārakaṃ caiva ilvalaṃ namuciṃ tathā|| 81.23||
vātāpiṃ cendradamanaṃ vipākaṃ pākam eva ca|
kālanemiṃ ca ṣaṇḍaṃ ca tathā cāmīsṛmuñjikam|| 81.24||
etān sarvān sa vivyādha daśabhirdaśabhiḥ śaraiḥ|
vikarṣatāṃ ca saṃgrāme ādityasrlaghuhastavān|
dhanūṃsi yugapaddevaściccheda ca nanāda ca|| 81.25||
tata eṣāṃ punarvāhān sūtān divyāñjayadhvajān|
prahasanniva viprendra sāyakairbahudhākarot|| 81.26||
te hatāśvā maheṣvāsā hatasūtāśca sarvaśaḥ|
vegena khaṅginaḥ sarve aṃśam evābhidudruvuḥ|| 81.27||
tān mūrttīniva śailendrān garjato jaladāniva|
asambhrāntastadādityo jānuṣvevāvapūrayat|| 81.28||
śarapūritagulphāste jānuṣveva ca dānavāḥ|
aṃśam utsṛjya vegena jagmuranyāṃ diśaṃ tadā|| 81.29||
tato devāstadā cakrurmahāntaṃ tūryanisvanam|
siṃhanādāṃśca vipulān bāhuśabdāṃśca puṣkalān|| 81.30||
aṃśo 'api āyamya bhagavān dhanurindrāyudhopamam|
dānavānāṃ sadaityānām akarot kadanaṃ mahat|| 81.31||
śirāṃsi dānavendrāṇām aṃśaḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|
apātayat phalānīva pakvāni śvasato yathā|| 81.32||
dhāvanti kecidaṃśena aśiraskāḥ śaraiḥ kṛtāḥ|
gatvā vegena saṃgrāmāt patanti ūrvyāṃ gatāsavaḥ|| 81.33||
apare bāhubhiśchinnairūrubhiśca mahābalāḥ|
patitā niṣṭanantyugraṃ nirayasthā yathā narāḥ|| 81.34||
śarapūritasarvāṅgāḥ śarasambaddhabandhanāḥ|
bhramanti tatra tatraiva saṃsāra iva dehinaḥ|| 81.35||
na sa tatrāsti daityo vā dānavo vā mahābalaḥ|
yaṃ śarā na viśantyugrā aṃśasya sumahātmanaḥ|| 81.36||
bandhujīvavanaṃ yadvadvanam ābhāti puṣpitam|
aśokakiṃśukānāṃ vā tathā daityabalaṃ babhau|| 81.37||
ayam aṃśo 'ayam aṃśeti netyayaṃ cāyam ityuta|
sarvam aṃśamayaṃ daityā hyapaśyanta bhayārditāḥ|| 81.38||
so 'api nityāyatadhanuḥ pariveṣīva bhāskaraḥ|
yaṃ yataḥ paśyate daityaṃ taṃ taṃ vivyādha patribhiḥ|| 81.39||
nādadānastadā hyaṃśaḥ sandadhānastathāpi vā|
na vikarṣan dhanuścaiva lakṣyate daityadānavaiḥ|| 81.40||
maṇḍalīkṛtam evāsya dṛśyante kārmukaṃ mahat|
āditya iva madhyāhne dṛśyate sa tadā yudhi|| 81.41||
sa divyacāpo laghuhastavān balī sadā mahāmaṇḍalabhūtakārmukaḥ|
dadāha śatrūn pavanerito raṇe vibhāvasuḥ śuṣkam ivendhanaṃ mahat|| 81.42||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddha ekaśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 81.81||

dvyaśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tāṃstathāṃśena daityendrān kālyamānānitastataḥ|
dṛṣṭvā balo mahāmāyo yantāram idam abravīt|| 82.1||
nayasva māṃ yato 'aṃśo 'ayaṃ durātmā dahate balam|
yāvadenaṃ śitairbāṇairnayāmi yamasādanam|| 82.2||
tasyāpatata evāṃśastadā praharatāṃ varaḥ|
dhvajaṃ ciccheda bāṇena hayāṃścaikaikaśastadā|| 82.3||
bhallena ca śiraḥ kāyādyanturāśu nyapātayat|
taṃ caiva pañcabhirbāṇairlalāṭe samaviddhyata|| 82.4||
tasya daityasya te bhānti lalāṭe pañca sāyakāḥ|
ghanodaraviniṣkrāntā bhāskarasyeva raśmayaḥ|| 82.5||
daityo 'api hi tadā dhanvī viyadutpatya roṣitaḥ|
sāyakairbahubhirvyāsa so 'aṃśaṃ samakiradbalī|| 82.6||
suvṛṣṭim iva jīmūtaḥ -- -- -- -- ivāśanim|
karān divākaro yadvat tuṣāraṃ candramā yathā|| 82.7||
tathā sa dānavo darpādbalaḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|
aṃśam evākirat tīkṣṇaiḥ sāyakairmarmabhedibhiḥ|| 82.8||
dhvajaṃ caivāsya ciccheda bahudhā dānaveśvaraḥ|
hayān vegahatān kṛtvā sārathiṃ cāpyasārathim|| 82.9||
kārmukaṃ bahubhirbāṇairvyadhama $I$-- -- -- -- --|
yathāṃśaṃ sa cakārograsthān yānapi daivatān|| 82.10||
nirudyamān mahāmāyaścakāra virarāsa ca|
kvacidgīṣpatisaṃkāśaḥ kvacidbhāskarasaṃnibhaḥ|| 82.11||
kvacit somāgnikalpaśca kvacit tārāgrahaiḥ samaḥ|
kvacit parvatasaṃkāśaḥ kvacidgṛdhravapurdharaḥ|| 82.12||
kvaciccākāśam āviśya adṛśyaḥ so 'asṛjaccharān|
śaropacitagātraṃ tacchinnaṃ bhinnaṃ vidāritam|| 82.13||
viṣṭabdhaṃ mūkavat sarvaṃ devānāṃ balam ābabhau|
naṣṭāvāditraninadaṃ hayaheṣitavarjitam|| 82.14||
gajabṛṃhitavimraṣṭaṃ śrāntayodhogranāditam|
niṣpandaṃ tadbalaṃ bhāti citrapratyarpitaṃ yathā|| 82.15||
ūrdhvaṃ nirīkṣate tatra yaḥ kaścidvibudho bale|
balastasya śarairvaktram akarodvi--vadbalī|| 82.16||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
ceṣṭāvirahitāścāsan yathā mokṣapathi sthitāḥ|| 82.17||
tāṃstathā sīdataḥ sarvān dṛṣṭvā balamahārṇave|
vāyurjayantaḥ pūṣā ca bhagaśca sumahābalāḥ|| 82.18||
nadantastāñcharāṃstasya balasya samavārayan|
vāyustasya mahābhāga śarān meghādivoditān|| 82.19||
muñcato mucyamānāṃśca muktāṃścaivāharadbalī|
bhago 'asya kārmukaṃ divyam acchinat prahasanniva|| 82.20||
dehatrāṇaṃ tathā pūṣā jayantaśca iṣudhī tathā|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 82.21||
samārdayañcharaistīkṣṇairdevā ravisamaprabhāḥ|
so 'ardyamānastadā devairbalī dānavapuṅgavaḥ|| 82.22||
vṛkṣaiḥ kānanajairvyāsa yuyudhe bhīmavikramaḥ|
tān drumāṃste tadākṣiptān balena bahudhā śubhān|| 82.23||
kracuḥ śarairdevatendrāstataḥ sa girim āvrajat|
gṛhītvā sa mahacchṛṅgaṃ samṛgavyālakinnaram|| 82.24||
cikṣepa sumahānādaṃ prakurvāṇo 'atidāruṇam|
tathā patan sa vegena pavano balavān balāt|| 82.25||
jahāra śṛṅgaṃ taccāpi papātāsuramūrdhani|
dānavānāṃ tadā koṭim ekāṃ vīryavatāṃ yudhi|| 82.26||
jaghāna balamuktaṃ tadgiriśṛṅgaṃ mahāsvanam|
tān hatān dānavāstena śṛṅgena ditinandanān|| 82.27||
dṛṣṭvā devāṃśca tānugrānabhajyanta sahasraśaḥ|
rathairaśvairgajaiścaiva tathā caiva padātayaḥ|| 82.28||
utsṛjya vāhanānyanye jīvitābhyarthinastadā|
pramuñcanto mahānādān palāyanta sahasrśaḥ|| 82.29||
dravatastāṃstadābhyetya hiraṇyākṣaḥ sa dānavaḥ| (?)
vipracittiśca danujaḥ prahlādaśca mahābalaḥ|| 82.30||
maya-- --ndhako daityastārakaḥ śakratāpanaḥ|
ūcire dānavān sarvān daityāṃśca bhayavihvalān|| 82.31||
bho bho dānavaśārdūlā daityāśca suraśatravaḥ|
kiṃ pālayatha tiṣṭhadhvaṃ mā bhayaṃ vo 'astu dānavāḥ|| 82.32||
kva gatā dānavā yūyaṃ sukhaṃ lapsyatha vā na vā|
ete balam ajānanto devāḥ pūrvaṃ mahābalāḥ|| 82.33||
na pramardanti pātāle sthitān nāpyasurottamāḥ|
niḥśeṣān pramathiṣyanti pātāle 'api kulādhamāḥ|| 82.34||
mā yāta vinivartadhvaṃ rirakṣiṣata sarvaśaḥ|
suyuddhenātmano daityā mā bhayaṃ vo 'atra jīvite|| 82.35||
kva gataṃ danujatvaṃ vaḥ kva gatā daityatā ca vaḥ|
kva ca vairaṃ suraiḥ sārdhaṃ kva rājyaharaṇaṃ gatam|| 82.36||
yaddhairyaṃ yaśca vo darpaḥ kulaṃ janma ca yaddhi vaḥ|
yacca vo garjitaṃ pūrvaṃ tasya kālo 'ayam āgataḥ|| 82.37||
tadā bruvata yaddaityā na bālā vayam ityuta|
vayam ekaikaśo yogyā devānāṃ nāśane 'api ca|| 82.38||
tasya kālo 'ayam adyeha prāptaḥ kiṃ vipalāyatha|
tat sarvaṃ garjitaṃ vo 'adya jānāmyaham ataḥ param|| 82.39||
śaradambudavaddaityā vyarthaṃ mā yāta bhīriha|
nivartadhvam adharmajñā yudhyadhvaṃ kṛtaniścayāḥ|| 82.40||
vīkṣadhvaṃ me saputrasya mahat karma kulādhamāḥ|
kaśyapasya sutaḥ śrīmān hiraṇyākṣo 'asmi dānavāḥ|| 82.41||
andhakaśca suto 'ayaṃ me brahmadattavaraḥ śubhaḥ|
hiraṇyakaśiporvīryaṃ yadabhūdasurottamāḥ|| 82.42||
dviguṇaṃ tanmamāpyasti vīkṣadhvaṃ tadaśaṅkitāḥ|
adya caitān mayā sarvān hatān paśyata dānavāḥ|| 82.43||
saṃgrāme yadi tiṣṭhanti sarve devā mamāgrataḥ|
adya trailokyam avyagraṃ hateṣvasuraśatruṣu|| 82.44||
vijvarā mokṣyatha sukhaṃ mayendreṇāsurottamāḥ|
mā vo 'astu bhayam adyeha yathā tiṣṭhanti sādhavaḥ|
saputraṃ māṃ yudhi yathā vīkṣamāṇāstu tiṣṭhata|| 82.45||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā viprendra gajāstottrārditā iva| gajāstotrā° Bh
vinivṛttāḥ punaḥ sarve lajjayātisamāvṛtāḥ|| 82.46||
te chatrasaṃchāditavaktrapadmā lajjāsamāviṣṭavirāgavaktrāḥ|
na tasya rājño mukhato 'avatasthustimerivārttāḥ salile 'alpamīnāḥ|| 82.47||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe 'asurākrośano nāma dvyaśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 82.82||

tryaśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha te dānavā vyāsa nivṛttā raṇamūrdhani|
duṣkaraṃ taṃ tadā cakrurvegaṃ nadya ivārṇave|| 83.1||
prahlādaścānuhlādaśca śinirbāṣakala eva ca|
virocano balirbāṇo balo 'anyo devakaṇṭakaḥ|| 83.2||
vipracittiśca ṣaṇḍaśca hradaśca saśatodaraḥ|
yamo 'asuraśca vyaṃsaśca śatāvartto hutodaraḥ|| 83.3||
keśī ca namuciścaiva tathendradamano 'asuraḥ|
mayo murastārakākṣo vidyunmālī prabhākaraḥ|| 83.4||
tāraśca tārakaścaiva bakaścāṭiśca viśrutaḥ|
mūkaścaiva kubhaścaiva kārtasvanamahāravau|| 83.5||
vātāpī celvalaścaiva tathaivelvakabalvalau|
ketuśca śataketuśca rāhuḥ svarbhānureva ca|| 83.6||
śambaro namuciścaiva kālaśambara eva ca|
dundubhirmahiṣaścaiva śatadundubhireva ca|| 83.7||
kālanemī vipākaśca pāko duryodhanastathā|
hastī sundanisundau ca śarabhaḥ kāla eva ca|| 83.8||
vṛṣaparvā śatākrandaḥ śatāvartto 'atha dhenukaḥ|
pralambaśca vakaścaiva gajo hālāhalastathā|| 83.9||
saiṃhikeyāśca vikhyātāḥ paulomāḥ kālakāsutāḥ|
nivātakavacāścaiva bāleyāśca tathā gaṇāḥ|| 83.10||
bāṇasya ca sutāḥ sarve kālakhañjāśca viśrutāḥ|
vṛtro vṛttaśca sagaṇastathānye sumahābalāḥ|| 83.11||
tasya sainyasya viprendra nardataḥ sambabhau tadā|
vegaḥ sa sindhurājasya velāṃ prati yathā mahān|| 83.12||
vāditraravasaṃmiśraiḥ siṃhanādaiḥ supuṣkalaiḥ|
rathanemihayānāṃ ca gajānāṃ bṛṃhitaiḥ saha|| 83.13||
sa śabdastumulo vyāsa trailokyam avapūrayat|
devā hyapi susaṃyattāḥ sarvodyogena saṃsthitāḥ|| 83.14||
pratyagṛhṇanta tān daityān krodhatāmrāyatekṣaṇāḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 83.15||
asibhiḥ pātyamānaiśca śataghnībhiśca sarvataḥ|
ulkābhiriva tadvyoma vicitram abhavat tadā|| 83.16||
śarāsibhinnakṛttāni patantyurvyāṃ śirāṃsi hi|
tālebhya iva pakvāni phalāni munisattama|| 83.17||
mukuṭairhākeyūraiḥ śroṇīsūtraiśca saprabhaiḥ|
niṣkairdukūlaiḥ kaṭakairaṅgulīyaiḥ sakuṇḍalaiḥ|| 83.18||
uracchadaiḥ kaṅkatībhiḥ karapālaiśca dantinām|
vyajanairbālavṛntaiśca chatrairmaṇibhireva ca|| 83.19||
paṭṭaiśca kāñcanairdivyaiḥ kavacaiśca mahāprabhaiḥ|
śirobhiścaraṇaiścaiva karairvaktrairmahāprabhaiḥ|| 83.20||
pratodaiśca kuthābhiśca yoktraiśca kanakojjvalaiḥ|
tatra yuddhaniśā bhāti tārābhirdyaurivāparā|| 83.21||
tiṣṭha tiṣṭha kva me yāsi nāsti mokṣastavādya vai|
sthito 'ahaṃ praharasveti na me bhīstiṣṭha me 'agrataḥ|| 83.22||
kiṃ garjasi vṛthā vyomni śaradīva balāhakāḥ|
karmaṇā darśaya kṣipraṃ garjitaṃ te 'adya niṣphalam|| 83.23||
naivaṃ prahriyate mūḍha mā vīkṣasva dṛḍho bhava|
tiṣṭha tiṣṭha kva gantāsi mama hatvā priyaṃ sutam|| 83.24||
sthito 'asmyeṣa nayiṣyāmi tvām adya yamasādanam|
adya ta --ratāṃ sarvāṃ devādhama suduḥsahām|| 83.25||
nāśayiṣyanti madbāṇāstiṣṭha tiṣṭha mamāgrataḥ|
dānavādhama devo 'asmi nāsmi bhīto 'aham āhave|| 83.26||
evaṃ vadanto yuyudhuryathā mattā mahāgajāḥ|
parasparavadhāsaktā yodhāstatra sahasraśaḥ|| 83.27||
anyonyam evam ābhāṣya praiṣayan yamasādanam|
siddhāśca cāraṇāścaiva vyomni sarve vyavasthitāḥ|| 83.28||
sādhayanti ramante ca nadanti ca yathāmbudāḥ|
mamāyaṃ dānavaḥ saṃkhye hato bhartā vinirmitaḥ|| 83.29||
ayaṃ devastava patirmā pārakye manaḥ kṛthāḥ|
kim evaṃ lobhayuktāsi śreṣṭhaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ parīkṣase|| 83.30||
svayaṃgraho na cehāsti lekhyaṃ vācaya mā tvara|
asaṃtuṣṭaṃ manaḥ kiṃ te saṃtuṣṭā bhava sundari|| 83.31||
bhāgo 'ayaṃ te surairdattastaṃ gṛhītvā vrajālayam|
evam apsarasaścātra vadanti ca hasanti ca|| 83.32||
samare nihate yodhe kurvanti kalahaṃ tathā|
mekhalāvalayonmiśraṃ tāsāṃ tat kalabhāṣitam|| 83.33||
śrutvā śrutvā ca te yodhā yuyudhurbhayavarjitāḥ|
valgitāsphoṭitaiścaiva diśaḥ sarvā vyanādayan|| 83.34||
tat pravāditagajopabṛṃhitavalgitākupitasiṃhanāditam|
devadānavabhayapravarttanaṃ jīvitāntakaram ābabhau raṇam|| 83.35||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe tryaśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 83.83||

caturaśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa yuddhayajñastatrāgryo rājyārtham abhavat tadā|
tatra yajvā svayaṃ devaḥ sahasrākṣaḥ pratāpavān|| 84.1||
saha devaiḥ surādhyakṣaḥ kuśāstasya śarā matāḥ|
āyudhāni vicitrāṇi sruvā yairhūyate haviḥ|| 84.2||
haviḥ prāṇāḥ samākhyātā agnirmṛtyurmahāprabhā|
mantrāścāstrāṇi divyāni puroḍāśāḥ śirāṃsyapi|| 84.3||
somastatra jayo 'abhūnnu rudrāścādhvaryavo 'abhavan|
ādityā bahvṛcaścāsan hotraṃ ca vasubhiḥ kṛtam|| 84.4||
brahmā samabhavaccātra svayaṃ devo bṛhaspatiḥ|
śāmitraṃ cāśvinau tau tu yajña evaṃ vyavarttata|| 84.5||
paśustatrābhavaddaityo hiraṇyākṣaḥ sahānugaḥ|
evaṃ babhau tadā yajño daityānāṃ śiśirādhipaḥ|| 84.6||
hiraṇyākṣo 'abhavadyajvā daityadānavanāyakaḥ|
vipracittirabhūddhotā prasthātāraśca dānavāḥ|| 84.7||
udgātā caiva prahlādaḥ śukro brahmā ca suvrataḥ|
paśurindraḥ sahasrākṣa evaṃ so 'ayajadavyayaḥ|| 84.8||
tasmiṃstadā mahāyajñe vartamāne mahābhaye|
indraḥ samāsadaddaityaṃ hiraṇyākṣaṃ mahābalam|| 84.9||
vāyurabhyāyayau tūrṇaṃ vipracittiṃ mahābalaḥ|
sakto 'abhūt saṃvareṇāṃśo balena bhaga eva ca|| 84.10||
virocanena pūṣā ca mitro balim athāsajat|
bāṇena varuṇaḥ sārdham andhakena yamaḥ saha|| 84.11||
jayantenelvalaḥ sārdhaṃ mayena saha candramāḥ|
ahirbudhnyena rāhuśca kāpālī śataketunā|| 84.12||
ajaikapāt kālanemiṃ jvaraḥ kārtasvanena ca|
prahlādenāryamā sārdham anuhlādena vai dharaḥ|| 84.13||
dhruvo hradena saṃsakto hyanye cānyairmahābalāḥ|
hiraṇyākṣastadendrasya dṛḍham āyamya kārmukam|| 84.14||
vivyādha gajam ekena kumbhadeśe mahābalaḥ|
devendraṃ pañcabhirbāṇairjatrudeśe samāhanat|
ṣaḍbhirlalāṭe vivyādha gajaṃ bhūyaśca saptabhiḥ|| 84.15||
sa gajastaiḥ śarairbhinnaḥ kṣaradrudhiram ābabhau|
gaurikāmbuparisrāvī śvetaḥ parvatarāḍiva|| 84.16||
tasya kruddhastadā śakro vajreṇa śataparvaṇā|
prahāram adadadvyāsa gaṇḍaveśe nanāda ca|| 84.17||
sa vajraghātaṃ daityendraḥ puṇyaghātam ivorjitam|
acintayānaḥ sagajaṃ śakram evārdayadbalī|| 84.18||
gajo 'api tena nirbhinnaḥ kṣaradrudhira ābabhau|
haviṣevānalaḥ krodhāt prajajāla jagarja ca|| 84.19||
sa vegaṃ mahadāsthāya aṅkuśena ca coditaḥ|
hiraṇyākṣarathaṃ tūrṇaṃ jagrāha rathakūbare|| 84.20||
gṛhītvā sa tam utkṣipya cikṣepa gajasattamaḥ|
meruśṛṅgam ivotkṣipya sameghaṃ śvetakuṇḍalī|| 84.21||
gatvā muhūrtaṃ vegena patan rathavaro babhau|
svarbhānunā hataḥ pūrvaṃ saratho bhāskaro yathā|| 84.22||
tatra samyak sthitaṃ bhūmau hiraṇyākṣarathaṃ punaḥ|
ājagāma gajastūrṇaṃ jighṛkṣurmunisattama|| 84.23||
prasāritakaro dantī stabdhadṛkkarṇavāladhiḥ|
abhyadhāvata vegena garutmāniva pannagam|| 84.24||
tam āpatantaṃ vegena samīkṣyāsurasattamaḥ|
babhāra sa tadā vyomni garutmāniva pannagam|| 84.25||
taṃ tu maṇḍalam āvṛttaṃ gajo 'apyanu tathaiva hi|
stabdhadṛkkarṇalāṅgūlaḥ prasāritakaro 'abhramat|| 84.26||
hāhākṛtam abhūt sarvaṃ sādhu sādhviti cobhayoḥ|
balayordevadaityānāṃ mūkavaccābhavat punaḥ|| 84.27||
sādhu daityeti cānyeṣāṃ hiraṇyākṣeti caiva hi|
sa gajaskandhago bhāti bhraman suragaṇeśvaraḥ|| 84.28||
sapakṣa iva śailendre mahiṣo 'agraṃ samāsthitaḥ|
hiraṇyākṣaśca daityendro bhramitvā trirmahāsuraḥ|| 84.29||
gajaṃ drutam ivotsārya rathe tasthau mahābalaḥ|
yudhyamānastu daityendro dṛḍham āyamya kārmukam|| 84.30||
devarājaṃ śaraistīkṣṇaiḥ samantāt paryavārayat|
sa taiḥ śaraistadā vyāsa marmasaṃdhiṣu tāḍitaḥ|| 84.31||
vajreṇa śatadhā tasya kavacaṃ pravyaśātayat|
hayānāṃ caiva yoktrāṇi sarvāṇyeva tākṛntata|| 84.32||
raśmīṃśca sūtahastasthān pratodaṃ caiva kāñcanam|
ciccheda bahudhā śakraḥ prahasanniva vīryavān|| 84.33||
chinnayoktrāstato 'asyāśvāḥ svacchandāḥ sampratasthire|
hiraṇyākṣo 'apyavaplutya gadayā samatāḍayat|| 84.34||
gajaṃ surapatiṃ caiva khaṅgena sa mahāsuraḥ|
sa gajastena ghātena tyaktvā taṃ rathasattamam|| 84.35||
śakṛnmūtraṃ sṛjan vyāsa prādravadbalavāṃstadā|
mardayāno nadaṃścaiva bhrāmayan surasattamam|| 84.36||
asinābhyāhataścāpi devarājo mahābalaḥ|
nārtimānabhavat saṃkhye na -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 84.37||
sa dānavendraprahatena dantinā mahābalaḥ prasrutadānagandhinā|
amṛṣyamāṇaḥ prayayau pramāthinā hiraṇyanetreṇa yudhi pramāthitaḥ|| 84.38||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe caturaśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 84.84||

caturaśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vipracittirmahāmāyo vāyuṃ bahubhirāśugaiḥ|
avākiraddanusuto vṛṣṭyeva hi jalapradaḥ|| 85.1||
saṃchādayaṃstadā vyāsa maṇḍalīkṛtakārmukaḥ|
iṣūṃścikṣepa tīkṣṇāgrāñchalabhān sāgaro yathā|| 85.2||
dhārā balāhakādyadvajjyotsnāścandramaso yathā|
raśmayo bhāskarādyadvaddhimaṃ himagireriva|| 85.3||
tathā te śarasaṃghātā dhanuṣo maṇḍalīkṛtāt|
vipracitterviniṣpetu -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 85.4||
bhāskaraṃ chādayānāṃstāñcharān āpatato balī|
bhagavānanilo vegādasureṣu nyapātayat|| 85.5||
taiḥ śaraistasya daityasya dānavā bahavo hatāḥ|
chinnāśca niṣṭanantyurvyāṃ nirayasthā yathā narāḥ|| 85.6||
tāṃstathā nihatān dṛṣṭvā vipracittirmahāsuraḥ|
avaplutya rathādvāyorbāhuyuddham ayudhyata|| 85.7||
tasya yuddhaprasaktasya vāyorbalam avardhata|
amanyanta surāścaiva nigṛhītaṃ danoḥ sutam|| 85.8||
athotpatya tadā vegādgadayā pavanaṃ dṛḍham|
atāḍayaddhiraṇyākṣo gaṇḍadeśe mahābalaḥ|| 85.9||
sa tena suprahāreṇa hiraṇyākṣasya -- -- --|
-- -- --nyanna kiṃcicca tata eva sa dānavam|| 85.10||
parityajya yayau tūrṇam anyadeśaṃ mahābalaḥ|
aṃśasaṃvarayoścāpi sumahanmunisattama|| 85.11||
yuddhaṃ samabhavadghoraṃ draṣṭR̥ṇāṃ tuṣṭivardhanam|
aṃśo 'asyāpatatastūrṇaṃ saṃvarasya mahābalaḥ|| 85.12||
darśaya/llāghavaṃ samyagdhvajaṃ ciccheda kāñcanam|
dhanuśca pañcadhā kṛtvā hayān ninye yamakṣayam|| 85.13||
tato 'asya sāratheḥ kāyācchiro bhūmāvapātayat|
bhūya enaṃ catuḥṣaṣṭyā sāyakānām avidhyata|| 85.14||
sa māyāṃ tāmasīṃ ghorāṃ samāviśyāśu dānavaḥ|
upalaiścāpi vajraiśca gadābhiḥ parighairapi|| 85.15||
kaṃkaṭaiḥ karavālaiśca bhindipālairayoghanaiḥ|
jaghāna sarathaṃ devam aṃśaṃ vyāsa raṇājire|| 85.16||
sa saṃdṛśya samantācca pātyamānaṃ mahābhayam|
aṃśo mūḍho raṇaṃ tyaktvā prayayāvanyato bhayāt|| 85.17||
bhago balaṃ samāsādya rathenāmbudanādinā|
tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti taṃ daityam uktvā vivyādha patriṇā|| 85.18||
sa sāyakaṃ samāsādya balo 'asuramahārathaḥ|
bhagaṃ hatastale tūrṇaṃ nirbibheda rarāsa ca|| 85.19||
tata enaṃ samāsādya māyayā prahasanniva|
āhatyorasi pādena svarathaṃ punarāvrajat|| 85.20||
tasya tallāghavaṃ śauryam amūḍhatvaṃ savīryatām|
dṛṣṭvā devāsurāḥ sarve sādhu sādhvityapūjayan|| 85.21||
bhago 'api lajjayāviṣṭaḥ padā tenāhatastadā|
muśalena hayāṃstasya rathaṃ caiva sasārathim|| 85.22||
nāmaśeṣāṃstadā kṛtvā vinanāda yathāmbudaḥ|
syandanaṃ tu balastyaktvā cūrṇitaṃ sahayaṃ tadā|| 85.23||
bhagasya kārmukaṃ divyaṃ bhūmisthaścācchinadbalī|
tata enaṃ pṛṣatkena lalāṭe samatāḍayat|| 85.24||
hastayośca punarvyāsa śarairvivyādha saptabhiḥ|
gṛhṇataḥ kārmukaṃ cāsya pṛṣṭhadeśe balo 'acchinat|| 85.25||
punaścānyat punaścānyat sa jagrāha tato bhagaḥ|
muśalaṃ kālamūlaṃ tat sarvaghātyanalaprabham|| 85.26||
hato 'asīti tam uktvaiva cikṣepa balanāśanam|
tam āpatantaṃ muśalaṃ balo dānavapuṅgavaḥ|| 85.27||
śarairviṣṭambhayāmāsa nandī mṛtyuṃ yathātmanaḥ|
atha pratihataṃ matvā muśalaṃ so 'asuraḥ punaḥ|| 85.28||
dhanuṣkoṭyā bhagaṃ mūrdhni balavān samatāḍayat|
rathaṃ ca saha sūtena gṛhītvā kūbare punaḥ|| 85.29||
cikṣepa dakṣiṇasyāṃ sa vāyurgirim ivārṇave|
pūṣā virocanaṃ devaḥ śarairbahubhirāśugaiḥ|| 85.30||
vivyādha samare kruddhaḥ sa ca taṃ pratyavidhyata|
saptabhirniśitairbāṇairiṣubhirmarmabhedibhiḥ|| 85.31||
kruddhaḥ pūṣā tathākṛṣya balavān kārmukaṃ mahat|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 85.32||
jīvitāntakaraṃ ghoraṃ yugāntādityavarcasam|
mumoca ripum uddiśya hatastvam iti cocivān|| 85.33||
tam āpatantaṃ bahudhā nadantaṃ diśaśca sarvā avabhāsayantam|
ulkāḥ sphuliṅgāśca samudgirantaṃ yayau ripūn vegavadutpatantam (?)|| 85.34||
sa cāpyavaplutya mahāsurendro dṛṣṭvā tam ādityasamānabhāsam|
matvāviṣahyaṃ svarathaṃ vihāya viyat samāviśya tato 'avatasthe|| 85.35||
tat tasya sūtaṃ hayopapannaṃ mahārathaṃ sarvagam astravaryam|
kṛtvāśu bhasmeva yathā hutāśo jagāma khaṃ divyam adṛśyarūpam|| 85.36||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe pañcāśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 85.85||

ṣaḍaśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato dagdharathaḥ khastho dānavaḥ sa virocanaḥ|
vegenāsiṃ viniṣkṛṣya sa pūṣṇo niśitāñcharān|| 86.1||
cicchedāpatataḥ sarvān kārmukaṃ caiva vīryavān|
tathā cainaṃ punarmūrdhni khaḍgena samatāḍayat|| 86.2||
sa tena suprahāreṇa kṣaradrudhiramastakaḥ|
rathopasthe papātāśu vṛttotsava iva dhvajaḥ|| 86.3||
patitaṃ taṃ sa daityendraḥ pragṛhyāśu mahābalaḥ|
cikṣepa devarājānaṃ nardamānaḥ payodavat|| 86.4||
baliṃ vivyādha mitraśca jatrudeśe śaraistribhiḥ|
balirekena bhallena tasya ciccheda kārmukam|| 86.5||
athainaṃ punaranyena hṛdaye samatāḍayat|
sa mūḍho mṛtakalpaśca rathopasthe sasāda ha|| 86.6||
taṃ sārathirmṛtyubhayādviṣaṇṇaṃ samupasthitam|
apovāha tadā vyāsa tato daityā vicukruśuḥ|| 86.7||
bāṇaṃ vivyādha varuṇaḥ pṛṣatkānāṃ śatena ha|
sa kārmukaśatāni sma pañca bāṇaḥ pratāpavān|| 86.8||
ākṛṣya yugapat kruddhaḥ śarāṃścikṣepa tāvataḥ|
tān āpatata evātha varuṇo laghuhastavān|| 86.9||
ekaikaṃ pañcadhā kṛtvā bāṇaṃ vivyādha pañcabhiḥ|
tato 'asya kārmukān sarvān varuṇaḥ prahasan balī|| 86.10||
ciccheda sāyakaistīkṣṇaistadadbhutam ivābhavat|
atha chinnadhanurdaityastasya cikṣepa vai gadām|| 86.11||
chinnāṃ dṛṣṭvā ca tāṃ bhūyo gadāḥ pañcāsṛjadbalī|
sa ekasyāṃ tadā saktastā gadā nābhyavaikṣata|| 86.12||
avikṣatāśca tāḥ sarvāḥ petustasya tatopari|
kācinmukuṭam āmardya nipapāta mahītale|| 86.13||
kācicca kārmukaṃ ghoraṃ hastadeśān nyapātayat|
kāciddhvajaṃ dṛḍhaṃ divyaṃ cikṣepa dharaṇītale|| 86.14||
kācidrathaṃ tadāhatya pāṃsugrāsaṃ cakāra ha|
urasi ūrūdare kaṭyām aparāstasya tā gadāḥ|| 86.15||
patantyaḥ sumahāghorā ārtiṃ cakrurmahābhayāḥ|
evaṃ sa tena virathaḥ kṛtaḥ kṛcchreṇa dhīmatā|| 86.16||
varuṇastaṃ samutsṛjya jagāmānyadraṇājiram|
yamo 'andhakaṃ samāsādya tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti coditaḥ|| 86.17||
atha tasya tato daṇḍaṃ rathaṃ prati samutsṛjat|
sa rathaṃ tasya saṃcūrṇaṃ kṛtvā śatasahasraśaḥ|| 86.18||
yamahastaṃ punargatvā tathaiva samatiṣṭhata|
andhako 'api rathaṃ tyaktvā gadāpāṇirmahābalaḥ|| 86.19||
yamaṃ samabhidudrāva krodhādvahnim ivotsṛjan|
sa tasya dhāvato vegāt pitṛrājo yamaḥ svayam|| 86.20||
daṇḍenaiva gadām ugrāṃ bhasmasāyujyam ānayat|
sa prahasya tadā cainam uvāca prasabhaṃ yamaḥ|| 86.21||
bhavato dhāma yadabhūt tat te vinihataṃ mayā|
sāmprataṃ tvām api punarneṣyāmyadya svam ālayam|| 86.22||
ahaṃ hi sarvalokasya maraṇe heturīśvaraḥ|
mayā vairaṃ samāsādya kvānte jīvaṃ vimokṣyase|
adya tvā nihaniṣyāmi sudṛḍhaṃ kriyatāṃ jagat (?)|| 86.23||
athavādya gato bandhaṃ pūrvaṃ cāndhaka matpuram|
agre draṣṭāsi tatraiva sarvānetān suradviṣaḥ|| 86.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
athaivaṃvādinaṃ yuddhe hyabhīto 'andhakadānavaḥ|
uvāca taṃ yamaṃ kruddhaṃ krodhāddīptānalekṣaṇaḥ|| 86.25||
hiraṇyākṣasuto dṛpto 'andhako 'asmi surāntakaḥ|
mahāyogabalopeto nāsmi prākṛtadānavaḥ|| 86.26||
aṅgādyena samutkṛtya bhāgān māṃsasya kārṣikān|
saṃvatsaraśatānyaṣṭau pañca caiva huto 'analaḥ|| 86.27||
tuṣṭo brahmā dadau yasya sadaivāmaratāṃ śubhām|
so 'ahaṃ nāmnā mahāsattvo mṛtyūtsedho na saṃśayaḥ|| 86.28||
na tvaṃ mama kṛto mṛtyuḥ siṃhasyeva vane śaśaḥ|
ahaṃ tu bhavitā mṛtyustava nāstyatra saṃśayaḥ|| 86.29||
adya tvāhaṃ durātmānaṃ sarvalokabhayaṃkaram|
hatvā śreyo vidhāsyāmi trailokyasyeti me matiḥ|| 86.30||
devānāṃ ca bhavān nityaṃ hantavyo vipriye sthitaḥ|
teṣām api priyo hyadya bhaviṣyati hate tvayi|| 86.31||
na tvayāsāditaṃ pūrvaṃ haratā jīvitāni hi|
kiṃcidbhūtaṃ mahadbhūtaṃ tena tvaṃ nirbhayaḥ sadā|| 86.32||
devāstava bhayādbhītā aśaktastvadvadhe tataḥ|
amṛtādīni lipyanti pūjayanti sadā ca te|| 86.33||
adya tvayi hate krūre nirdvandvāste 'api sāmarāt|
amṛte na tathā prītiṃ kariṣyanti na saṃśayaḥ|| 86.34||
adya garvaṃ ca darpaṃśca yogamāhātmyam eva ca|
prāṇaiḥ sahaiva dehānte nāśayiṣyāmi sarvaśaḥ|| 86.35||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam asurendreṇa tarjito bhāskarātmajaḥ|
daṇḍenāsuraśārdūlam uttamāṅge 'abhyatāḍayat|| 86.36||
kālaśca taṃ kareṇaiva hṛdaye samatāḍayat|
mṛtyuścāśaninā kṣipraṃ śirasyevābhyatāḍayat|| 86.37||
kaṇṭhe ca niyatistasya pāśaṃ cikṣepa dāruṇam|
kṛtāntaḥ parighenaiva gaṇḍadeśe samāhanat|| 86.38||
sa tairamoghairyāmaiśca prahato 'andhakadānavaḥ|
puṣpavṛṣṭyā yathā kaścidārtimānabhavat tathā|| 86.39||
na pāśāstasya līyante daṇḍo vā parigho 'api vā|
anyāni cāsya tīvrāṇi na duḥkhāya bhavantyuta|| 86.40||
tataḥ sarvaistadotkruṣṭaṃ dānavaiḥ sarvatodiśam|
avādyanta ca tūryāṇi mumude cāndhako bhṛśam|| 86.41||
sa teṣāṃ tuṣṭiśabdena madavīryasamīritaḥ|
vinadyāmbuvadvyāsa yamam evābhidudruve|| 86.42||
sa gatvā tasya vegena hanyamāno 'api kiṃkaraiḥ|
ājaghāna mahāvego muṣṭinorasi taṃ yamam|| 86.43||
punaśca mahiṣaṃ tasya śirasyabhihanat padā|
tāvubhau vihvalau tatra bhramitvā kiṃcidantaram|| 86.44||
hitvāndhakaṃ tatastūrṇaṃ yayaturmunisattama|
jayantaścelvalaṃ prāpya vivyādha daśabhiḥ śaraiḥ|| 86.45||
tasyelvalaścakartāśu dhvajaṃ ratnavibhūṣitam|
hayānāṃ caiva yoktrāṇi pratodaṃ caiva kāñcanam|| 86.46||
vinā yoktrairhayāstasya rathaṃ tyaktvā samuddhatāḥ|
lānā vijagmurheṣanto jayanto viratho 'abhavat|| 86.47||
sa rathaṃ samparityajya bhūsthaḥ śakrātmajaḥ prabhuḥ|
ilvalasya hayān sūtaṃ dhvajaṃ caiva nyapātayat|| 86.48||
athobhau virathau bhūtvā hyanyonyavijayaiṣiṇau|
avidhyetāṃ tadā yasya kārmuke sāyakaiḥ śitaiḥ|| 86.49||
parasparavinirmuktānubhau saṃvārya sāyakān|
astrairastrāṇi saṃvārya nedatuḥ sāgarāviva|| 86.50||
atha śakrasutaḥ śrīmā/llabdhvā tasya tadāntaram|
dhanuściccheda bhallena nanāda ca punaḥ punaḥ|| 86.51||
sa vikṛttadhanurdaityaḥ khaḍgaṃ dīptānalaprabham|
bhrāmayitvā vicikṣepa tam apyasyācchinat tadā|| 86.52||
gṛhītvānyasya patitāṃ gadāṃ hemavibhūṣitām|
bhrāmayitvā tu cikṣepa sāpadudrāva vegavat|| 86.53||
sa yāvat tāṃ gadāṃ ghorāṃ śaraiḥ sannataparvabhiḥ|
viciccheda diteḥ putrastāvadasyācchinaddhanuḥ|| 86.54||
atha yāvat sa nistriṃśaṃ jagrāhāditinandanaḥ|
tāvadenaṃ padā daityo vāmenorasyatāḍayat|| 86.55||
tam eva tasya jagrāha pādaṃ sa ca mahābalaḥ|
jayanto bhrāmayaccainaṃ nardamāno yathāmbudaḥ|| 86.56||
tato hāhākṛtam abhūdasurāṇāṃ bale mahat|
yāta trāyata daityendram ilvalaṃ śīghram ityuta|| 86.57||
devānāṃ siṃhanādāśca śaṅkhaśabdāśca puṣkalāḥ|
tūryāṇi cāpyavādyanta sādhu sādhviti cābhavat|| 86.58||
jayanto 'api yathā cakraṃ vidhātā balavāṃstadā|
bhrāmayāmāsa daityendraṃ yugāntāmbudavannadan|| 86.59||
atha svayaṃ hiraṇyākṣaḥ so 'andhako balireva ca|
bāṇo 'atha vipracittiśca śambaro 'atha virocanaḥ|| 86.60||
kālakeyāśca te daityāḥ paulomāḥ siṃhikāsutāḥ|
nivātakavacāścainaṃ samantāt paryavārayan|| 86.61||
sa taiḥ śarairgadābhiśca parighairdīrghavedhanaiḥ|
anyaiśca bahubhiścitrairāyudhaiḥ prahato bhṛśam|| 86.62||
sa hanyamānastaṃ devo jayantaḥ śakranandanaḥ|
hiraṇyākṣapathe kṣiptvā prādravadyena devatāḥ|| 86.63||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe ṣaḍaśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 86.86||

saptāśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
mayaścandramasaṃ devam ārdayat krodhamūrcchitaḥ|
śarairāśīviṣākārairnardamāno yathāmudaḥ|| 87.1||
tasyāsyatastato bāṇāṃścandramāḥ prahasanniva|
ekaikaṃ saptadhā kṛtvā mayaṃ vivyādha pañcabhiḥ|| 87.2||
tata enaṃ pṛṣatkena lalāṭe samavidhyata|
jahāsa ca puno devastasya lajjāṃ samādadhat|| 87.3||
sa tasya hasataḥ śīghraṃ lalāṭe kaṅkapatriṇā|
vivyādha bhṛśam āyasto yathā vighno yatavratam|| 87.4||
tato 'asya deva uddiśya dhvajaṃ ciccheda nādayan|
cakrarakṣāṃśca nistriṃśairanayadyamasādanam|| 87.5||
tasya taccāpalaṃ vīkṣya mayo dānavasattamaḥ|
māyāṃ divyāṃ samāsthāya rāhuḥ samabhavat tadā|| 87.6||
sa rāhubhūto daityendro deveśaṃ śaśalakṣaṇam|
abhyadravadyathā rāhuu rathenāmbudanādinā|| 87.7||
sa tāṃ māyāṃ tadā jñātvā devo hyamṛtasambhavaḥ|
aparvavadviyatsthaṃ vai taṃ śaraistribhirārdayat|| 87.8||
so 'api daityo mahāmāyastāñcharān māyayaiva tu|
vārayannabhidudrāva śītaraśmiṃ mahāsuraḥ|| 87.9||
tato 'asya syandanaṃ divyaṃ nāgayantṛ mahāprabham|
gṛhītvā kūbare daityaścikṣepa ca rarāsa ca|| 87.10||
ahirbudhnaḥ samāsādya rāhuścandramaso graham|
viśikhaiḥ pañcabhirviddho dhvajam asya nyapātayat|| 87.11||
tasyotpatya rathādrāhurgadayā bhīmarūpayā|
dhanurdhvajaṃ hayāṃścaiva samacūrṇayadavyayaḥ|| 87.12||
aśaniṃ śataghaṇṭāṃ sa dīptāṃ mṛtyoriva snuṣām|
jagrāha bhṛśam āyastaḥ pāśaṃ mṛtyorivāntakaḥ|| 87.13||
bhrāmayitvā sa tām ugrāṃ yamadaṇḍanibhāṃ balāt|
cikṣepa rāhum uddiśya vidyutaṃ megharāḍiva|| 87.14||
sā jvalantī maholkeva meghāśanirivojjvalā|
papāta rāhoḥ śirasi yathā vajraṃ śiloccaye|| 87.15||
atha tena prahāreṇa nārtimānabhavat sa vai|
sa prahasya bhṛśaṃ rāhurvegaṃ cakre mahābalaḥ|| 87.16||
ahirbudhnaṃ prati kruddhā nāgānām iva pakṣirāṭ|
āpatantaṃ sa vīkṣyaiva bhagavān devasattamaḥ|| 87.17||
jagāma tasya panthānaṃ muktvānyena yathoragaḥ|
śataketuśca taṃ vīro rathenāmbunādinā|| 87.18||
abhyadravadraṇe kruddhastiṣṭha tiṣṭheti cābravīt|
ādhāvato 'asya kāpālī hṛdayaṃ kaṅkapatribhiḥ|| 87.19||
bibheda kuliśaḥ kṣipto giriśṛṅgam ivocchritam|
sa bhinnahṛdayastena rudreṇa grahasattamaḥ|| 87.20||
papāta svarathe mūḍhaḥ śakradhvaja ivocchritaḥ|
tato hāhākṛtaṃ daityairgṛhṇa gṛhṇeti cāpyuta|| 87.21||
sādhu sādhviti devāśca vinedurjaladā iva|
athāndhako hiraṇyākṣo vipracittirvirocanaḥ|| 87.22||
śambaraścelvalaścaiva bāṇo balirathāpi ca|
kālakeyāḥ sapaulomā nivātakavacāśca ye|| 87.23||
anye ca bahavo daityāstaṃ rudraṃ paryavārayan|
te śaraiśca gadābhiśca muśalaiḥ prāśatomaraiḥ|| 87.24||
nyavārayanta taṃ devaṃ tarjayantaḥ punaḥ punaḥ|
sa hanyamānastairdevo bahubhirmunisattama|
apāsartata vegena samīpāt suravidviṣām|| 87.25||
ajaikapāt kālanemiṃ gadinaṃ gadayāsaham|
samāhvayata daityendraṃ madhuṃ viṣṇurivorjitam|| 87.26||
tau suyuddhau gadāhastau maṇḍalāni mahābalau|
anyonyavijaye saktau grahāviva viceratuḥ|| 87.27||
kālanemistu saṃkruddho gadāṃ hemapariṣkṛtām|
śataghaṇṭāṭṭahāsāṃ ca mṛtyorjihvām ivādbhutām|| 87.28||
bhrāmayitvāsakṛddaityo nardamāno yathā vṛṣaḥ|
mumoca rudram uddiśya skandaḥ śaktim ivācale|| 87.29||
śakramuktām ivāyāntīm aśaniṃ parvatopari|
vidyutaṃ vā mahāśaktāṃ sa rudro bhīmavikramaḥ|| 87.30||
vañcayāmāsa vegena śveto mṛtyum ivāgatām|
tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti cāpyuktvā rudraḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|| 87.31||
bhrāmayitvā gadāṃ ghorāṃ daityasyoparyapātayat|
sa tayā gadayā daityo dīptayā bhīmarūpayā|| 87.32||
hato mūrdhni diśaḥ sarvā hāridrāḥ samapaśyata|
atha daityastadā samyagbhrāmayan sa gadāṃ punaḥ|| 87.33||
maṇḍalāni vicitrāṇi darśayitvā mahābalaḥ|
ajaikapādaṃ gadayā skandhadeśe vyatāḍayat|| 87.34||
sa cāpyavahatastena yathā vajreṇa bhūdharaḥ|
viveśa bhūmiṃ duḥkhārttastadadbhutam ivābhavat|| 87.35||
utthāya ca sa vegena rudraḥ kruddho mahābalaḥ|
avasavyaṃ caran daityasavyato maṇḍalecaraḥ|| 87.36||
bhrāmayitvā gadāṃ bhūyo daityasyoparyapātayat|
sa daityastena ghātena bhramitvā trirmahābalaḥ|| 87.37||
saṃstabhya gadayā bhūyo rudraṃ kukṣāvatāḍayat|
sa tayā gadayā nunno yathā vāyvīrito nagaḥ|| 87.38||
papāta bhūmau vegena śataśṛṅgo yathā purā|
patitaṃ tu tato 'abhyetya pade jagrāha suvratam|| 87.39||
bhrāmayitvā ca cikṣepa sa cāmṛtyuravasthitaḥ| (?)
kārtasvanaṃ jvaraścogro rudraḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|| 87.40||
jaghāna niśitairbhallairdaśabhiḥ stanayoḥ samam|
kārtasvanaśca bāṇena kārmukaṃ tasya dīptimat|
ciccheda bahudhā cainaṃ punarvivyādha patribhiḥ|| 87.41||
-- -- -- -- --rudro 'api daṇḍaṃ sarvārthasādhakam|
bhrāmayitvāśu cikṣepa kārtasvanarathaṃ prati|| 87.42||
taṃ yugāntānalaprakhyaṃ śatasūryānalaprabham|
jaghāna śarajālena megho vṛṣṭyā yathācalam|| 87.43||
hanyamānaśca tairdaṇḍo haviṣeddha ivānalaḥ|
bhūyastaraṃ prajajvāla vegavaccāpyadhāvata|| 87.44||
tam apratihataṃ daṇḍaṃ jñātvā kārtasvanaḥ sa tu|
ratham utsṛjya vegena ākāśastho 'abhavadbalī|| 87.45||
daṇḍaśca ratham abhyetya sahayaṃ saha yantṛṇā|
sadhvajaṃ sapātakaṃ ca bhasma kṛtvā yayau punaḥ|| 87.46||
yāvaddaṇḍo na patati rathenaiti ca taṃ prati|
tāvat kārttasvano rudraṃ śarairabhyadravadbalī|| 87.47||
chittvā dhvajaṃ dhanuścāsya tathā yoktrāṇi vājinām|
virathaṃ taṃ jvaraṃ kṛtvā asinā mūrdhnyatāḍayat|| 87.48||
asighātaparītātmā sa rudraḥ śatrusaṃsadam|
tyaktvānyato yayau tūrṇaṃ padātirmunisattama|| 87.49||
so 'asighātaviparītacetano raktacandanavilepanaprabhaḥ|
taṃ vihāya ripum agryavikramaṃ dudruve surabalaṃ yatastataḥ|| 87.50||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe saptāśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 87.87||

aṣṭāśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
aryamā bahubhirbāṇaiḥ prahlādaṃ daityapuṅgavam|
ājaghāna rathaṃ ghoraṃ dhvajaṃ cāsya vyaśātayat|| 88.1||
prahlādo 'apyaryamantaṃ vai rathaṃ tyaktvaiva vīryavān|
pradudrāva yathā rāhuḥ samaye timirāpaham|| 88.2||
ādhāvantaṃ ca vegena vihastaṃ ripum aryamā|
jaghāna bahubhirbāṇairvṛṣṭyā megho yathācalam|| 88.3||
śarānagaṇayanneva hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ|
krodhānmānācca darpācca vegena samadhāvata|| 88.4||
gṛhītvā kūbare tasya rathaṃ hemapariṣkṛtam|
citrepa saha sūtena tato harṣānnanāda ca|| 88.5||
anuhrādo dharaṃ prāpya tena viddhaḥ stanāntare|
asiṃ niṣkṛṣya vegena dharasya ratham āsadat|| 88.6||
dhvajaṃ tasya hayāṃścaiva sārathiṃ dhanureva ca|
chittvā skandhe dharaṃ caiva punaḥ svaratham abhyagāt|| 88.7||
karmaṇā tena daityasya dharo 'abhūdbhṛśam arditaḥ|
evam anyaiśca daityendrairanye devā mahābalāḥ|| 88.8||
nirjitāstarjitāścaiva yuddhāya ca punaḥ sthitāḥ|
tataḥ saṃkulam evābhūddevānāṃ dānavaiḥ saha|| 88.9||
parasparajigīṣūṇāṃ yuddhaṃ bhīrubhayāvaham|
tato bheryaśca śaṅkhāśca paṭahāsekyapuṣkalāḥ|| 88.10||
jharjharyaḥ pepukāścaiva ḍiḍṇimā goviṣāṇakāḥ|
avādyanta bale vyāsa ubhayeṣāṃ sahasraśaḥ|| 88.11||
tato 'asṛgoghapravahā patākadhvajapādapā|
gajāśvagrāhabahulā rathapravarakacchapā|| 88.12||
keśaśaivālabahulā dhanurjyākṛtatantukā|
niṣṭanacchastramaṇḍūkā dukūlacchatraphenilā|| 88.13||
uṣṇīṣavarahaṃsā ca karapādaśiropalā|
hārakeyūrasikatā mukuṭotphullapaṅkajā|| 88.14||
medosrakaphapaṅkā ca prāṇajīvitanāśinī|
prāvartata nadī ghorā hastyaśvarathavāhinī|| 88.15||
tasyāṃ snāyanti rakṣāṃsi pibanti ca ramanti ca|
nṛtyanti cāpi vividhāsbhīrūṇāṃ bhayadāstathā|| 88.16||
gṛdhrā gomāyavaścaiva śvāno mārjāravāyasāḥ|
cakṣūṃṣi karapādāntraṃ bhakṣayanto 'abhiremire|| 88.17||
mamāyaṃ hastinaḥ pādo mamāyaṃ medapaṭṭakaḥ|
mamāyaṃ ca karaḥ śukro bāhuśca rudhirasyadaḥ|| 88.18||
mamāyaṃ tava nāyaṃ ca gṛhṇa paśyeti caiva hi|
kalahaṃ cakrire tatra krūrāḥ piśitabhojanāḥ|| 88.19||
tyaktvānye ca hatāṃstatra svadehān sumahārathāḥ|
vimānaiḥ strījanākīrṇaiḥ prayayurbrahmaṇaḥ sadaḥ|| 88.20||
apare pāpakarmāṇo hanyamānā ruṣāndhitaiḥ|
patanti narake ghore krandamānā muhurmuhuḥ|| 88.21||
kecidārttasvaraṃ kṛtvā -- -- -- -- --ṣārditāḥ|
mriyante puruṣā yuddhe śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|| 88.22||
daśantaśca tṛṇānyanye bhrātaḥ putreti cāpare|
krandamānā janā bhītāḥ prāṇān kṛcchreṇa tatyajuḥ|| 88.23||
saṃdaṣṭauṣṭhapuṭāḥ keciddevāsuramahārathāḥ|
śarasannatamarmāṇaḥ patantyurvyāṃ drumā iva|| 88.24||
aśivāni śivā neduraṭṭahāsāṃśca rākṣasāḥ|
ārttanādāṃśca puruṣāstathaiva gajavājinaḥ|| 88.25||
siṃhanādāśca śūrāṇāṃ bāhuśabdāśca puṣkalāḥ|
dhanuṣāṃ kṛṣyamāṇānāṃ śabdā vādyaravāstathā|| 88.26||
athendraśca dhaneśaśca yamaḥ kālaśca vīryavān|
varuṇo marutaścaiva viśvedevāśca sarvaśaḥ|| 88.27||
mitraścaiva jayantaśca bhagaḥ pūṣāryamā tathā|
kāpālī cāpi yo rudro vasavaśca mahābalāḥ|| 88.28||
nāsatyaścaiva dasraśca pṛśnayaśca surottamāḥ|
ete cānye ca devānāṃ pravarā bāhuśālinaḥ|| 88.29||
dānavānāṃ bale vegaṃ balavanto 'abhicakrire|
sāgarā iva garjanto yugānte analā iva|| 88.30||
prabhañjanā ivākāle mahānta iva cācalāḥ|
vṛṣabhā iva nardanto bṛṃhanta iva kuñjarāḥ|| 88.31||
grasantaśca yathā grāhāśchindanto makarā iva|
varṣamāṇā iva ghanāḥ siṃḥā iva ca nardinaḥ|
dānavānāṃ balaṃ sarve vegenaivābhyavārayan|| 88.32||
taddevavegaprahatābhivegaṃ balaṃ sayatnaṃ danudānavānām|
bhavatyanādhāram atiprasaktaṃ tṛṇaṃ yathā vahnimukhāvasaktam|| 88.33||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe aṣṭāśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 88.88||

ekonanavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tadveganunnānāṃ bhagnānāṃ kliśyatāṃ punaḥ|
trāṇārtham atidīptākṣo hiraṇyākṣo 'agrahīt padam|| 89.1||
andhakaśca mahāmāyo bhrātaraścāsya tatsamāḥ|
śataṃ rathasahasrāṇāṃ sarveṣām apalāyinām|| 89.2||
prahlādaśca sahabhrātā hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ|
vipracittiḥ sahabhrātā saiṃhikeyaiśca taiḥ saha|| 89.3||
gṛhṇa gṛhṇeti nardanto devān pratyudyayustadā|
teṣāṃ teṣāṃ ca saṃgrāmaḥ sughoraḥ samapadyata|| 89.4||
grāhāṇām iva kāṇḍe ca gajānām iva vā vane|
indrastvaṣṭā ca pūṣā ca hiraṇyākṣam avārayan|| 89.5||
saṃgatya sāyakaistīkṣṇaiḥ sarvamarmasvatāḍayan|
teṣāṃ dhanūṃṣi citrāṇi asyatāṃ ca divaukasām|| 89.6||
māyābalena daityendro vyaṣṭambhayata dīptimān|
tāni viṣṭambhitāni sma tadā daityena māyayā|| 89.7||
nānamanti yathā pūrvaṃ tataste hi ākulābhavan|
so 'api daityo mahāmāyo naditvā meghanisvanam|| 89.8||
babandha teṣāṃ gātrāṇi samantādastramāyayā|
tān baddhāṃśca samīkṣyaivam akarmaṇyān mahābalān|| 89.9||
yantāro vāhanaiḥ kṣipraṃ jahnustambhādraṇājirāt|
atha kālo yamaścaiva dhaneśo mitra eva ca|| 89.10||
varuṇo vasavaḥ sarve aśvinau ca mahābalau|
pragṛhītāyudhāḥ kruddhāstiṣṭha tiṣṭheti vādinaḥ|| 89.11||
abhyadravanta vegena hiraṇyākṣaṃ mahāsuram|
teṣām āpatatāṃ saṃkhye sa daityaḥ krodhamūrcchitaḥ|| 89.12||
sarveṣāṃ sāyakaistīkṣṇairbibheda kavacān yudhi|
te bhinnakavacāḥ sarve krodhāt prajvalitānanāḥ|| 89.13||
sasarjurastramukhyāni tadāpratihatānyuta|
yamo daṇḍaṃ sasarjāsya tathā kālaśca -- -- --|| 89.14||
dhaneśaścāśaniṃ ghoraṃ varuṇaḥ pāśam eva ca|
bhagaśca muśalaṃ ghoram anye cānyāṃstathāmarāḥ|| 89.15||
tān sa daityo hasanneva sāyakairmarmabhedibhiḥ|
vyaṣṭambhayadadīnātmā śakrahastaṃ yathā bhavaḥ|| 89.16||
sādhuvādāṃstato hṛṣṭā dānavānāṃ mahārathāḥ|
samaṃ cakruśca sampūjya hiraṇyākṣaṃ mahāsuram|| 89.17||
apare naitadāścaryaṃ ditiputrasya saṃyuge|
kaśyapena prasūtasya rājño 'asmākaṃ ca svāminaḥ (?)|| 89.18||
apare siṃhanādāṃśca bāhuśabdāṃśca puṣkalān|
cakrurhṛṣṭāśca vādyāni tathā sarvāṇyavādayan|| 89.19||
evaṃ hi samprahṛṣṭānāṃ dānavānāṃ mahāhave|
pārāśarya giro bahvyaḥ śrūyante stuti-- -- --|| 89.20||
teṣāṃ praharṣaṃ jñātvetthaṃ devabhaṅgaṃ ca taṃ tadā|
sarvaprāṇicaro vāyurasurānabhidudruve|| 89.21||
sahasranalvamātreṇa sa rathena prabhañjanaḥ|
samantāddhvajayuktena patākāśatamālinā|| 89.22||
javena yantR̥ṇāṃ yatnānnigṛhītena śabdavān|
prapūrayan diśaḥ sarvāḥ sahasā pratyadṛśyata|| 89.23||
sa pañcabhiḥ śaraistīkṣṇairdaityarājam athāvyayaḥ|
āhatya yojane tasmāddeśāt kṣipram avāsṛjat|| 89.24||
andhakaṃ ca tataḥ ṣaṣṭyā vipracittiṃ ca saptabhiḥ|
mayaṃ pañcāśatā viddhvā saptabhiḥ saptabhiḥ punaḥ|| 89.25||
daityāṃśca dānavāṃścaiva sarvān vivyādha tatkṣaṇāt|
punaḥ pulomaputrāṃśca nivātakavacānapi|| 89.26||
te tena bahubhirviddhāḥ śarairasurapuṅgavāḥ|
dikṣu sarvāsu vikṣiptā yojanāntaritāḥ sthitāḥ|| 89.27||
yān yāṃśca te vimuñcanti gadāmuśalapaṭṭiśān|
tān sarvān bhagavān vāyurdānavoparyapātayat|| 89.28||
te hatā hanyamānāśca svamuktairāyudhairbhṛśam|
ārtanādān prakurvāṇāḥ prādravanta diśo diśaḥ|| 89.29||
so 'api vāyurmahāvego babhañja rathasattamān|
pāṃśuvarṣeṇa ca punaścakṣūṃṣyeṣām apūrayat|| 89.30||
tataste bhayasaṃtrastā notsasarjustadā śarān|
śastrāṇi ca tathānyāni puñjaśaścāvatsthire|| 89.31||
tasya tat karma saṃvīkṣya hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca dānavān sarvān garhayan ditinandanaḥ|| 89.32||
dhigvo daityā balaṃ sarvaṃ dhigdarpā dhik parākramāḥ|
visṛjya raṇam avyagrā yāta strīkarma sevata|| 89.33||
ye yūyaṃ raṇamadhyasthā jīvite sati bāliśāḥ|
ekena vāyunā bhagnā dhigvastanmantritaṃ purā|| 89.34||
athavā yanmayā proktaṃ yūyaṃ bālā ratiklamāḥ|
tat tathā nāsti saṃdeho bālairiva hi vaḥ kṛtam|| 89.35||
tiṣṭhadhvaṃ bālavat sarve rakṣanto jīvitaṃ svakam|
aham eko vijeṣyāmi vāyum enaṃ prapaśyata|| 89.36||
tataḥ sa parvato bhūtvā ditiputraḥ pratāpavān|
samantādvāyuvegaṃ taṃ samavārayadavyayaḥ|| 89.37||
-- -- --$i$tvānilaṃ jñātvā parvatena nivāritam|
andhako bāhupāśena avaplutyābabandha tam|| 89.38||
sa baddho bāhupāśena tadā vāyuḥ pratāpavān|
sampragṛhyāndhakaṃ śīghram utpapāta vihāyasā|| 89.39||
tasyotpatitamātrasya pragṛhyāndhakadānavam|
rāhurgadāṃ mahāraudrāṃ kṣipraṃ mūrdhni nyapātayat|
abhyetya pādayoścaiva vipracittirmahābalaḥ|| 89.40||
jagrāha sumahāgrāho matsyāniva mahārṇave|
sa tena suprahāreṇa vihvalaḥ prāṇigocaraḥ|| 89.41||
skandhe keśābhisaṃyukto bhrāmito vipracittinā|
sa bhrāmyamāṇo vibabhau srastahārasragambaraḥ|| 89.42||
alātam iva saṃdīptaṃ niśāyāṃ munisattama|
bhrāmyamāṇaṃ samālakṣya punardevāḥ savāsavāḥ|| 89.43||
vegaṃ cakrurmahāvegā gṛhṇa gṛhṇeti vādinaḥ|
vipracittistu tān daityaḥ saṃrabdhānudyatāyudhān|| 89.44||
ālakṣya subahūn saṃkhye garjamānaḥ payodavat|
abhīkṣṇaṃ bhīmasaṃhrādaṃ vāyuṃ dānavayūthapaḥ|| 89.45||
cikṣepa śakram uddiśya girau vajraṃ yathaiva saḥ|
sa cāpi tena vikṣipto labdhasaṃjño mahābalaḥ|| 89.46||
vidhāya vegaṃ devendram upatasthe kṛtāñjaliḥ|
tato vāyuśca devāśca sarva eva sahānugāḥ|| 89.47||
abhyadravanta daityendrān pragṛhītavarāyudhāḥ|
teṣāṃ teṣāṃ ca saṃgrāmaḥ sughoraḥ samapadyata|| 89.48||
siṃhānām iva dṛptānāṃ vijane śarabhaiḥ saha|
tatra kecidvinihatāḥ suprahāreṇa mūrcchitāḥ|| 89.49||
sādhu sādhviti bhāṣantaḥ prāṇān ūrdhvaṃ vitatyajuḥ|
apare danudaityendrā mudā yuktā mahābalāḥ|| 89.50||
pareṇābhyāhataṃ śūraṃ samarakṣan suputravat|
keciddhatvāpi subahūn devadānavasattmāḥ|| 89.51||
avikṣatāḥ śitaiḥ śastrairātmānaṃ garhayantyuta|
aśastraṃ kecidabhyetya devadaityā mahābalāḥ|| 89.52||
dharmayuddham abhīpsantastyaktvā śastrāṇyayodhayan|
bahavastatra daityendrā yuyudhurbhīmavikramāḥ|| 89.53||
devāśca nāhatā ye vai nābhighnanti kadācana|
padātayastatra sarve yodhayanti padātibhiḥ|| 89.54||
sādinaḥ sādibhiḥ sārdhaṃ rathino rathibhiḥ saha|
gajino gajibhiścaiva tathā yuddham avartata|| 89.55||
evaṃ teṣāṃ hi saṃgrāmo devānāṃ dānavaiḥ saha|
āvartata śatānyaṣṭau varṣāṇi sumahābhayaḥ|| 89.56||
atha daityo mahāmāyo gajenāmbudavarcasā|
tomaraṃ sumahadbibhradyugāntānalavarcasam|| 89.57||
kokilāñjanameghābho vidruto yo virocanaḥ|
so 'abhyadravat tadā devān ātisavyānivotthitān(?)|| 89.58||
sa gajena prabhinnena mukhāḍambaraghoṣiṇā|
abhidudrāva devendraṃ tiṣṭha tisṭheti cābravīt|| 89.59||
tasyāpatata evātha bhagavān pākaśāsanaḥ|
jatrudeśe śaraṃ ghoraṃ nicakhāna rarāsa ca|| 89.60||
anubhūya prahāraṃ taṃ sa daityo bhīmavikramaḥ|
tasyāsya tomareṇātha bibheda karam unnatam|| 89.61||
athāsya tomarodbhinnāddhastāddhemavibhūṣitam|
papāta taddhanurdivyaṃ mahāśanisamaprabham|| 89.62||
tato 'asya bhūyo daityendro vyākulasya tadā gajam|
tomareṇa bibhedāśu kumbhadeśe mahābalaḥ|| 89.63||
sa bhinnastena daityena vane matta iva dvipaḥ|
anaṅkuśaḥ śanairghṛ-- svaṃ balaṃ hyanivāritaḥ (?)|| 89.64||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
te tathā vadhyamānāstu ādityā daityadānavaiḥ|
bhayārditā diśaḥ sarvāḥ palāyante sma sarvaśaḥ|| 89.65||
tataḥ śaṅkhāśca bheryaśca vādyāni vividhānyapi|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
siṃhanādāṃśca saṃcakrurdaityadānavasaṃmatāḥ (?)|| 89.66||
tacchinnabhinnapravidāritāntaraṃ gajena daityaiśca punarviloḍitam|
balaṃ mahaddaivatapālitaṃ babhau yathārṇavo mandaramanthavikṣataḥ|| 89.67||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddha ekonanavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 89.89||

navatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
taddevasainyaṃ saṃdṛśya daityadānavayūthapaiḥ|
vadhyamānaṃ bhṛśaṃ vyāsa vyādhairiva mṛgān vane|| 90.1||
timirārirmahātejāḥ somaḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|
tigmavarṣmā suśītārciḥ svayaṃ pavanasārathiḥ|| 90.2||
tau baddhakavacau samyak śarāsanadharāvubhau|
baddhagodhāṅgulitrau ca tathā baddheṣudhī ca tau|| 90.3||
sakhaḍgau ca saghaṇṭau ca sapatākau gajāviva|
ubhau vīrau mahāvīryau yoddhuṃ daityān vyavasthitau|| 90.4||
somastu daśabhistīkṣṇaiḥ sāyakairmarmabhedibhiḥ|
vivyādha hṛdaye daityaṃ hiraṇyākṣaṃ mahāsuram|| 90.5||
sa bhinnahṛdayo daityaḥ somena dṛḍham uddhataḥ|
mohaṃ samāviśadvyāsa krauñcaḥ śattyaiva parvataḥ|| 90.6||
taṃ tathābhisamīkṣyaiva rathaṃ yantā sahāsuram|
apovāha mahāmāyaṃ dhaneśaṃ nidhayo yathā|| 90.7||
tato hāhākṛtaṃ daityairdaivataiḥ sādhu sādhviti|
gṛhṇa gṛhṇeti daityaiśca mā gṛhṇeti ca daivataiḥ|| 90.8||
tato bheryaśca śa"mkhāśca paṇavā goviṣāṇakāḥ|
avādyanta surāṇāṃ vai harṣarāgapravartanāḥ|| 90.9||
athāndhakaśca tāraśca tārako namucistathā|
vipracittiḥ śaṃvaraśca mahāmāyaśca dānavaḥ|| 90.10||
dhundhuḥ kārtasvanaścaiva rāhuścaiva mahābalaḥ|
śataketuḥ śatāvartaḥ pulomā vilvalastathā|| 90.11||
vātāpī kālanemiśca śatāvartaḥ śatodaraḥ|
mahāpārśvodaraścaiva musuṇḍaḥ suṇḍa eva ca|| 90.12||
durlomā vakrabandhaśca viromā rodha eva ca|
mārīcaśca subāhuśca śvetakuṇḍalireva ca|| 90.13||
vṛṣaparvātikāyaśca śarabhaḥ siṃha eva ca|
narāntako devahanastathā yajñahanaśca yaḥ|| 90.14||
daityau sundanisundau ca śakratāpana eva ca|
prahlādaśca anuhlādaśca śinirbāṣkala eva ca|| 90.15||
virocano balirbāṇo vātāśvaśca mahābalaḥ|
mayo 'atha tārakākṣaśca vidyunmālī prabhākaraḥ|| 90.16||
dundubhirmahiṣaścaiva ariṣṭo riṣṭa eva ca|
keśī ca dhenukaścaiva ajako vyaṃsa eva ca|| 90.17||
tathā gaganamūrdhā ca asilomā ca dānavaḥ|
sūcīlomā tuhuṇḍaśca huṇḍaśca paratāpanaḥ|| 90.18||
hastī duryodhanaścaiva vipākaḥ pāka eva ca|
balo muro 'atha narako mūkendradamanāvapi|| 90.19||
aśvagrīvaḥ sambaraśca tathānyaḥ kālasaṃvaraḥ|
śālvaḥ śatabhujaścaiva drumo vyāghraśca dānavaḥ|| 90.20||
madhuśca kaiṭabhaścaiva mahāsaṅgara eva ca|
chāyāgrahaśca vikhyātaḥ saiṃhikeyāśca viśrutāḥ|| 90.21||
hālāhalāśca te sarve baliputrāśca viśrutāḥ|
tathā mayasutāḥ sarve nivātakavacāśca ye|| 90.22||
paulomāḥ kālakeyāśca vipracittisutāśca ye|
ete cānye ca bahuśo daityadānavasaṃmatāḥ|| 90.23||
sarve candrasamaṃ devaṃ prati vegaṃ pracakrire|
mahiṣā iva -- -- -- hastinaḥ śarabhaṃ yathā|| 90.24||
vighnā yataprataṃ yadvat kāmā mokṣāśritaṃ yathā|
indriyārthā yathā yogam anarthā duḥkhitaṃ yathā|| 90.25||
nāgā iva garutmānaṃ bhramarā iva pādapam|
tathā te dānavāḥ sarve pragṛhītavarāyudhāḥ|| 90.26||
dudruvuḥ śiśiraṃ devaṃ mahājaladanisvanāḥ|
teṣām āpatatāṃ vyāsa timirārirhasanniva|| 90.27||
udyatāni āyudhāni sma śaraiściccheda sarvaśaḥ|
tataḥ sa tān punardevaḥ sarvāneva ruṣānvitaḥ|| 90.28||
hṛdayeṣu śaraistīkṣṇairbibheda ca rarāsa ca|
tuṣāreṇa ca śītena tārādhipatiravyayaḥ|| 90.29||
ājaghānāsurān sarvān krodhasaṃraktalocanaḥ|
te śaraiśca vinirbhinnāḥ śītena ca bhṛśārditāḥ|| 90.30||
sthitāstatraiva daityendrāścitrapaṭṭārpitā iva|
candro 'api devaḥ samare maṇḍalīkṛtakārmukaḥ|| 90.31||
bibheda sarvān daityendrān nardamānaḥ payodavat|
yaḥ kaściddānavo vāpi daityo vā munisattama|| 90.32||
sarva eva śarāṃstasya dadhire śa'sinastadā|
yat kiṃciccālayatyaṅgaṃ tatra daityaḥ kadācana|| 90.33||
tat tat tīkṣṇaiḥ śarairdevo bibheda ca rarāsa ca|
bruvato daityayodhasya yatra kvacana saṃyuge|| 90.34||
nicakhāna śarānaṣṭau mukhe tasyāpi candramāḥ|
śaranirbhinnasarvāṅgāścitrapaṭṭārpitā iva|| 90.35||
yathā sa bhagavān devaścandramā dānavārdanaḥ|
tathaiva bhagavān vahnirārdayaddānavān yudhi|| 90.36||
tadrathāśvagajayodhasaṃyuktaṃ prakṣaradrudhirabinduvihvalam|
sīdate gajakulopamaṃ balaṃ paṅkalagnam iva sarvam ulvaṇam|| 90.37||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe navatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 90.90||

ekanavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasmin bale tathā tena somenāpratimaujasā|
hanyamāne mahāmāyaḥ samāśvasya tadāsuraḥ|| 91.1||
hiraṇākṣo diteḥ putra idam āha ruṣānvitaḥ|
garutmanaḥ sutaṃ vīraṃ rathayantāram āhave|| 91.2||
khageśvara na te lajjā bhavatīha raṇārṇave|
yanmāṃ rathena saṃgrāmāt tvaṃ harasyanyato 'adya vai|| 91.3||
kiṃ vakṣyantyasurāḥ sarve daityāścaiva mahābalāḥ|
rājāsmākaṃ jitaḥ saṃkhya śatrubhiḥ śatrutāpanaḥ|| 91.4||
jīvitaiṣī parityajya bālānasmān durātmavān|
raṇādapagataḥ kvāpi dhiṅmām aśubhakāriṇam|| 91.5||
kaśyapasya suto bhūtvā bhrātā daityasya saṃmataḥ|
hiraṇyakaśipordaityo mahāyogabalānvitaḥ|| 91.6||
agrataḥ sarvadaityānāṃ dānavānāṃ tathaiva ca|
rājā svāmī ca śūraśca nirjitaḥ śatrubhiḥ katham|| 91.7||
athavā devapakṣasya tvaṃ putro vai garutmataḥ|
tam eva pakṣaṃ bhajase na māṃ tvaṃ parirakṣase|| 91.8||
nāhaṃ tava na śakto 'adya śiraḥ kāyāt sakuṇḍalam|
khaḍgenānena tīkṣṇena chettuṃ khagakulādhama|| 91.9||
mitraṃ tvaṃ mama mandasya purā bālasakheti ca|
ataḥ kṛtvābhirakṣāmi gaccha mukto 'asi doṣavān|| 91.10||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā rathayantā khageśvaraḥ|
uvāca ślakṣṇayā vācā hiraṇyākṣaṃ mahāsuram|| 91.11||
mā krudho dānavaśreṣṭha nāsmi daitya tavāhitaḥ|
tadopavāhitaḥ kṣipraṃ raṇādrakṣārtham eva hi|| 91.12||
sūtāḥ śāstravidaścaiva bruvate dānaveśvara|
dampatī rathiyantārau parasparam anuvratau|| 91.13||
rathinā śastraghātebhyo rakṣyo yantā yathā priyā|
tena caiva ratho rakṣyo yathā bhartā jayāvahaḥ|| 91.14||
sa bhavān ripuṇā bhinno hyavabaddhaśca saṃyuge|
aśaktaḥ syāditītyevaṃ mayā kṣipram apohitaḥ|| 91.15||
āśvasya balam ādhāya punaryuddhena daṃśitaḥ|
ripūñjeṣyasi saṃgrāme tvevaṃ tvam apavāhitaḥ|| 91.16||
ye hi kāle 'apayānti sma kāle cāyānti daṃśitāḥ|
teṣāṃ nāsulabho daitya jayo yuddhe mahātmanām|| 91.17||
na cāham ahitaḥ satyaṃ hitakṛt tava nityadā|
mā śaṅkāṃ kuru daityendra śape satyena sarvataḥ|| 91.18||
na cāpyaviditaṃ te 'adya kṛto yacchapathaḥ purā|
tathaiva mṛtapaścāhaṃ na mṛtyurmama vidyate|| 91.19||
ahaṃ garutmanaḥ putro devān hitvāsurāñchritaḥ|
tavaiva daitya snehena mā śaṅkāṃ tvaṃ kṛthā mayi|| 91.20||
etadbalaṃ candramasā vahninā copapīḍitam|
trāhi kṣipraṃ mahābāho na śokaṃ kartum arhasi|| 91.21||
māyām atha samāsthāya dhanuṣā vā balena vā|
jahi śatrūn mahārāja mā ruṣantu diteḥ sutāḥ|| 91.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa taṃ pariṣvajya pakṣirājaṃ mahāsuraḥ|
abhidudrāva vegena rathenāmbudanādinā|| 91.23||
tasyāpatata evātha savahniścandramāstathā|
śarairāśīviṣākārairdhvājaṃ cicchidaturyudhi|| 91.24||
tato lalāṭe vidhvainaṃ tau devau śaśipāvakau|
yugāntāmbudavadvyāsa nādam uccaiḥ pracakratuḥ|| 91.25||
tayostallāghavaṃ dṛṣṭvā hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
āgneyenāstramukhyena śiśiraṃ tadvyaśātayat|| 91.26||
tuṣāravarṣaṇaṃ dagdhvā tato 'asau māyayā punaḥ|
saṃmohayitvā vegena rāhurbhūtvābhidudruve|| 91.27||
sa rāhuṇā tadā tena grasyamānaḥ khageśvaraḥ|
raṇaṃ tyaktvānyato yātastato daityo nanāda ha|| 91.28||
dānavā hyapi te sarve naṣṭe tasmin himāśaye|
samāśvasya punaścakruryuddhaṃ suragaṇaiḥ saha|
te 'ambudāśanisannādāḥ samudrasamanāditāḥ|| 91.29||
daityadānavamahārathāḥ pravarasādina āśvasantaḥ|
-- -- taneva yuddhakāṃkṣiṇo daṃṣṭriṇa iva mahāgajā vanasamāśritāḥ|| 91.30||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddha ekanavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 91.91||

dvinavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
nakṣatrādhipatiṃ dṛṣṭvā bhagavān havyavāhanaḥ|
vidrutaṃ dānavabhayāt padātiryoddhum udyataḥ|| 92.1||
sa śarairdānavarathaṃ sasūtaṃ sahavājinam|
sadhvajaṃ sapatākaṃ ca bhasmasāyujyam ānayat|| 92.2||
tato 'asya kārmukaṃ divyaṃ śareṇānataparvaṇā|
vijyaṃ cakāra saṃkruddhastiṣṭha tiṣṭheti cābravīt|| 92.3||
athāndhakaśca rāhuśca prahlādo maya eva ca|
anye ca dānavaśreṣṭhāḥ kuśānuṃ paryavārayan|| 92.4||
so 'avaplutya tadā teṣāṃ dhanūṃṣi ca rathāṃstathā|
dhvajāni ca vicitrāṇi dadāha ca rarāsa ca|| 92.5||
kavacāni vicitrāṇi śirāṃsi ca vasūttamaḥ|
dadāha vikṛtākāro nādayan sarvato diśaḥ|| 92.6||
hā heti nadatāṃ tatra bhagavān havyavāhanaḥ|
jihvā dahan babhau vyāsa guhāyāṃ dīptavat sthitaḥ|| 92.7||
keṣāṃcit pradahaṃstāni dānavānāṃ mukhāni saḥ|
paṅkajānīva phullāni timirārirmahāprabhaḥ|| 92.8||
keṣāṃcit tu gajendrāṇāṃ karān kāñcanabhūṣitān|
dadāha bhagavān vahnirdāvāgnirbhujagāniva|| 92.9||
śarāñcharāsanāṃścaiva tathā khaḍgaparicchadān|
dadāha bhagavān vahnirhastyaśvam api sarvaśaḥ|| 92.10||
te hanyamānā daityendrā viśastrā duḥkhitā bhṛśam|
bhramanti vitanutrāśca tatra tatraiva -- -- --|| 92.11||
teṣāṃ vahnipradīptānāṃ dahyatāṃ suravidviṣām|
hiraṇyākṣaḥ svayaṃ rājā parjanyaḥ samapadyata|| 92.12||
sa meghabhūto daityendrastam agniṃ vṛṣṭibhistadā|
praśāmayata vegena saṃvartaka ivāmbudaḥ|| 92.13||
taṃ praśāntaṃ tadālakṣya vidhuraṃ havyavāhanam|
vipracittiḥ śaraistīkṣṇairlalāṭe samavākirat|| 92.14||
tato 'asya nadato bhūyo mayo dānavasattamaḥ|
mukhe śarān mahāghorān nicakhāna mahāsuraḥ|| 92.15||
tasya tena tadā vyāsa mukhe bhinnasya dāruṇaḥ|
uttasthau vāyuvaddhūmaḥ śarīrādañjanopamaḥ|| 92.16||
tena dhūmena khaṃ caiva divaṃ bhūścaiva sarvaśaḥ|
pūritā mahatā vyāsa na prajñāpayata kiṃcana|| 92.17||
tena śabdena saṃjñābhirnāmaviśrāvaṇairapi|
karasparaśaistadānyonyam anayadyamasādanam|| 92.18||
na devo jñāyate tatra na daityo dānavo 'api vā|
ajānantastatastatra saṃsthām etāṃ pracakrire|| 92.19||
āṭiṃ daityāḥ prakurvanta vaka ityeva devatāḥ|
bakaṃ vadanti ye tatra daityāstān vyahanaṃstadā|| 92.20||
āṭiṃ bruvāṇasṃ ca surā ityevaṃ tadvyavartata|
evaṃbhūtam abhūdyuddhaṃ varṣāṇāṃ tu sahasrakam|
mahadbhayaṃ vai daityānām andhakāre suraiḥ saha|| 92.21||
tadandhakāre sumahābhayaṃkaraṃ tadābhavadyuddham atīva dāruṇam|
jagadvināśāya jagaddhitaiṣiṇāṃ surāsurāṇāṃ rudhiraughanisravam|| 92.22||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddha dvinavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 92.92||

triṇavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
athāsau tena kālena keturagneḥ samutthitaḥ|
vāyunābhihitaścaiva agacchadvilayaṃ bhṛśam|| 93.1||
tataḥ samabhavadvyoma vimalaṃ sarvam eva hi|
apaśyanta surāḥ sarve daityāścaiva parasparam|| 93.2||
tataḥ śaṅkhāśca bheryaśca paṭahāḍambarāstathā|
sughoṣakā ḍiṇḍimāśca bhagnā bheryaśca sarvaśaḥ|| 93.3||
baladvaye 'apyavādyanta śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|
atha śakraśca devendro yamo vaiśravaṇastathā|| 93.4||
pūṣā bhagaśca dvāvetau aryamā mitra eva ca|
jayanto marutaścaiva rudrādityāśca sarvaśaḥ|| 93.5||
vegena sumahāvegā mamṛdurdānavaṃ balam|
tatra cāmīkarābhāsaṃ pragṛhya balavaddhanuḥ|| 93.6||
yamo daṇḍena daityendrānanayadyamasādanam|
sa pañcabhiḥ śarairviddhvā hiraṇyākṣaṃ mahābalam|| 93.7||
aśvāṃścaikaikaśaḥ sarvāñjahāsa ca nanāda ca|
tasya sarve tadāyastā daityadānavasattamāḥ|| 93.8||
śarān āśīviṣākārān vyasṛjan vikṛtāśanān|
tān sa ciccheda samare tridhaikaikaṃ laghukriyaḥ|| 93.9||
punaśca viśikhairghorairardayat prahasanniva|
tato 'andhakasya yantāraṃ rathaṃ ca saha vājibhiḥ|| 93.10||
kiṃkareṇa mahāvīryo yamo ninye svakaṃ puram|
tato 'andhako gadāpāṇiryugāntāmbudavannadan|| 93.11||
abhyadhāvadyamaṃ tūrṇaṃ tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti cābravīt|
tasya vajreṇa devendro gadāṃ hemapariṣkṛtām|| 93.12||
bibheda śatadhā vyāsa sāpatadbhuvyavasthitā|
taṃ viśastraṃ vikavacaṃ kṛtvā te devasattamāḥ|| 93.13||
yugapacchastravarṣeṇa tāḍayāmāsurāhave|
yamo daṇḍena taṃ mūrdhni śakro vajreṇa cāhanat|| 93.14||
vittado 'aśaninā caiva pāśena varuṇastathā|
anye cānyaistathā devā hyamoghairāyudhottamaiḥ|| 93.15||
abhyadhāvannasaṃrabdhā hatastvam iti vādinaḥ|
na caiva tasya daityasya duḥkhaṃ tatrābhavat tadā|| 93.16||
so 'api daityastatotpatya puṇḍasyāsthāya pṛṣṭhataḥ|
yamaṃ muṣṭiprahāreṇa puṇḍādbhūmāvapātayat|| 93.17||
tathendrasya gajaṃ bhūyaḥ pucche saṃgṛhya vegavān|
bhrāmayitvākṣipaddūre naṣṭastvam iti cābravīt|| 93.18||
tato dhaneśasya punaḥ śivikāṃ kāmagāminīm|
ākṣipya bahudhā daityo vyadhamat krodhamūrchitaḥ|| 93.19||
tato gajairgajān nighnat padātīṃśca padātibhiḥ|
rathaṃ rathena ca raṇe hayāṃśca hayasādibhiḥ|| 93.20||
punargaje mahendrasya hanyamāno 'api saṃyuge|
samutplutya tadā śakraṃ gajaskandhānnyapātayat|| 93.21||
tasya tat karma saṃvīkṣya dānavendrasya saṃyuge|
sarve devā diśaḥ sarvāḥ pranaṣṭā jīvitārthinaḥ|| 93.22||
pūrveṇa bhagavānindraḥ sahādityaḥ salokapaḥ|
dakṣiṇena tathā rudrā vasavaścāśvināvapi|| 93.23||
pratīcīṃ takṣarakṣāṃsi piśācāḥ pannagaiḥ saha|
uttareṇa tathānye ca prapadyanta yathā mṛgāḥ|| 93.24||
teṣu bhagneṣu daityendrāḥ pṛṣṭhato vikṛtāyudhāḥ|
abhyadhāvanta garjanto bhayaṃ teṣāṃ vyadarśayan|| 93.25||
tato muhūrtaṃ te gatvā hiraṇyākṣeṇa vāritāḥ|
nivṛttāḥ samatiṣṭhanta sarve 'amarṣavaśaṃ gatāḥ|| 93.26||
athovāca tataḥ kruddhān hiraṇyākṣo hasanniva|
daityadānavanāthāṃstānidaṃ vacanakovidaḥ|| 93.27||
kim ebhirabalairadya yuṣmākaṃ daityadānavāḥ|
avabaddhaiśca ruddhaiśca mṛtasaṃjñairdurātmabhiḥ|| 93.28||
hatāste nātra saṃdeho yeṣāṃ rājyam idaṃ dhṛtam|
naiṣāṃ jīvitam adyāsti mā tvaradhvaṃ subāliśāḥ|| 93.29||
abalānapi saṃrabdhān nirāśāñjīvitaiṣiṇaḥ|
avadhyeti balāccaiva durjayāśca na saṃśayaḥ (?)|| 93.30||
saṅgamokṣannidānīṃ ca la -- -- -- -- -- sava (?)|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- ityuvāca sadośanāḥ (?)|| 93.31||
yadetadrājyam iti āhuḥ prāṇā hyete mahātmanām|
sa teṣāṃ harati prāṇān yasteṣāṃ rājyam āharet|| 93.32||
teṣām adya hṛ-- -- -- -- -- -- tamasaiḥ suraiḥ|
āpūrayāma sthānāni devānāṃ dānaveśvarāḥ|| 93.33||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste sahiraṇyākṣāḥ prāviśannamarāvatīm|
ratnāni jagṛhurvyāsa vijayaṃ cāvaghoṣayan|| 93.34||
ārakṣam āmanustatra cakṣurāptaiśca te 'asurāḥ|
āśvāsayanta paurāṃśca tathā prakṛtayaśca ha|| 93.35||
-- -- m iti tathārgheṇa tathaivopāyanairvaraiḥ|
āśīrbhiścāsuraśreṣṭhaṃ hiraṇyākṣaṃ praṇemire|| 93.36||
tān samāśvāsya daityendro hyadhyasya ca varāsanam|
kāryāṇi kṛtvā sarveṣām agacchadvaruṇālayam|| 93.37||
te siṃhanādairvividhaiśca vādyaiḥ pravalganāsphoṭitakūjitaiśca|
mahāsurā dānavarājasiṃhaṃ jagmuḥ samantāt parivārya sarve|| 93.38||
|| iti skandapurāṇe varuṇālayagamane triṇavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ||
93 ||

caturṇavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tam āpatantaṃ vegena garutmantam ivāhave|
dṛṣṭvā varuṇaputrāste pitrā saha vidudruvuḥ|| 94.1||
daityāścāpi hi te sarve prāpya tadvaruṇālayam|
vyūḍhaskandhā vyatiṣṭhanta vyasṛjaṃstat puraṃ prati|| 94.2||
dūtaṃ vātāpinaṃ caiva rājñā preṣitam ūrjitam|
sa gatvā tāṃ purīṃ ramyāṃ praviśya ca mahāsuraḥ|| 94.3||
pauraiḥ supūjito vyāsa prāhedaṃ tān sugarvitaḥ|
rājā sarvasya lokasya daityadānavanandanaḥ|| 94.4||
kaśyapasya sutaḥ śrīmān hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
jitvā sarvān surān saṃkhye ājñāpayati vaḥ sadā|| 94.5||
yūyaṃ śṛṇuta sarve me ājñāṃ kuruta caiva hi|
ānayadhvaṃ ca ratnāni parityajata devatāḥ|| 94.6||
devapakṣo 'atra yaḥ kaścit pure prativasatyuta|
abhayaṃ tasya yacchāmi yātu devānabhītavat|| 94.7||
nāradādyāśca ṛṣayastaṃ samāsādya daityakam|
ūcustam asuraṃ vyāsa sāntvayuktam idaṃ tadā|| 94.8||
rājā bhojo virāṭ samrāḍbhūpatiḥ kṣatriyo nṛpaḥ|
ya ebhiḥ stūyate śabdaiḥ kastannārcayate budhaḥ|| 94.9||
sa tvaṃ rājā ca bhojaśca virāṭ samrāṭ tathaiva ca|
bhūpatiḥ kṣatriyaścaiva nṛpaḥ sarvasahastathā|| 94.10||
nirjitāḥ sumahāvīryāstvayā devāḥ savāsavāḥ|
kastvayā sadṛśo loke bāhyaikaṃ rudram īśvaram|| 94.11||
tvaṃ pātā sarvalokānāṃ hartā sraṣṭā tathaiva ca|
kastavājñāṃ mahārāja pratihanyāddurātmavān|| 94.12||
vayaṃ ca sarve daityendra varam icchāma dānava|
varadastvaṃ hi bhūtānām asmākaṃ varado bhava|| 94.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā varado 'asmīti so 'abravīt|
ūcuste daityarājānaṃ tadā vacanakovidāḥ|| 94.14||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ|
yadetaduktaṃ bhavatā narakavyādhimṛtyuṣu|
na tathā tadbhaveddaitya eṣsa no dīyatāṃ varaḥ|| 94.15||
daitya uvāca|
mama pratijñā viprendrāḥ pūrvam eva tapodhanāḥ|
lokānāṃ sukhamedheyaṃ rājā lokasya yadyaham|| 94.16||
na tathā tat kariṣyāmi yadyahaṃ munisattamāḥ|
mithyāpratijñaḥ syāṃ cāham asatyaśca durātmavān|| 94.17||
tasmādanyadbhavanto māṃ varaṃ yācantu supriyam|
kartāsmi taṃ tathā sarvaṃ yāce 'ahaṃ śirasā hi vaḥ|| 94.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā ṛṣayaḥ sarva eva te|
hiraṇyākṣam idaṃ vyāsa punarevābruvan vibhum|| 94.19||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ|
lokadharmapravṛttyarthaṃ brahmaṇā daityapuṃgava|
kṛtam etat purā sarvaṃ dharmaścāpi pravartitaḥ|| 94.20||
samīkṣya caitallokasya dharmaścāpi pravartitaḥ|
nābhūtastadbhaveddaitya iti no varado bhava|| 94.21||
pratijñā prabhavet sā yallokānāṃ suḥkhavarjanam|
tacca tasmānna naśyeta brahmaṇaḥ kṛtiravyayā|| 94.22||
yāvat tvaṃ daitya lokasya rājā hyasi prabhuśca ha|
evaṃ tvayānṛṇatvaṃ ca brahmaṇaḥ adya kṛtaṃ bhavet|| 94.23||
teṣāṃ sa vacanaṃ śrutvā ṛṣīn niścitya daityarāṭ|
ye drohāḥ śakrapāśāśca mamājñābhaṅgakāriṇaḥ|| 94.24||
teṣām eva bhavenmṛtyurnarakeṣu ca yātanāḥ|
etadāha tadā rājā te cāpi ūcurnarādhipam|| 94.25||
evam astviti tāṃścoktvā yātanāmokṣam ādiśat|
sa muktvā nārakān sarvān dadau sthānasya rakṣaṇam|| 94.26||
pitṛrājānam anagha vipracittiṃ mahābalam|
tato 'avaghuṣya sa jayaṃ pūjayitvā tu tān dvijān|
jagāma dhanadāvāsaṃ hiraṇyākṣo mahābalaḥ|| 94.27||
te tāṃ dhaneśasya purīṃ mahābalā vinādayanto 'andhakapālitāstadā|
hiraṇyanetraṃ parivārya dānavāstadābhijagmurjaladā ivācalam|| 94.28||
|| iti skandapurāṇe hiraṇyākṣadigvijaye yamalokābhigamano nāma
caturṇavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 94 ||

pañcanavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tathā laṅkāṃ samāsādya dhaneśasya purīṃ śubhām|
adūre tasthuruddhūtāḥ sannaddhakavacāyudhāḥ|| 95.1||
avasthitāṃstathā dṛṣṭvā dānavān baladarpitān|
laṅkānivāsinaḥ sarve nidhipālāstathaiva ca|| 95.2||
nidhayaḥ śaṃkhapadmādyā ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
arghaṃ ratnāni cādāya dānavāya nyavedayan|| 95.3||
ūcuśca tava daityendra vayaṃ vaśyā na saṃśayaḥ|
kiṃkarāśca praśādhyasamān yathāvaddānaveśvara|| 95.4||
hiraṇyākṣa uvāca|
mā bhīrbhavatu vo yakṣā mama yūyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ|
ayaṃ rājā hi vaḥ śreṣṭho hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ|| 95.5||
prahlādo devasaṃghānāṃ sarveṣāṃ viprabādhanaḥ|
tatastaṃ tatra saṃsthāpya dhaneśaṃ daityapuṃgavam|| 95.6||
anyeṣāṃ devasaṃghānāṃ sthānāni āpūrayat punaḥ|
saṃsthāpya sarvasthāneṣu sthānino dānaveśvarān|| 95.7||
andhakastvamarāvatyām indratvenābhyaṣecayat|
bhūrlokaṃ cākhilaṃ daityaḥ svayam evānvaśāsata|| 95.8||
bhūyaśca dhanurādāya saśaraṃ sūryasannibhaḥ|
daityendro medinīṃ prāha mamātmānaṃ vidarśaya|| 95.9||
sā bhītā tasya daityasya vepamānā kṛtāñjaliḥ|
jayetyuktvāgratastasthau viṣṇorlakṣmīrivāparā|| 95.10||
tāṃ mṛgīm iva śārdūlo bhujaṅgīm iva pakṣirāṭ|
śārdūlīṃ siṃha iva ca siṃhīṃ śarabharāḍiva|| 95.11||
haṃsīṃ kāka iva kṣudro mayūrīṃ madgurāḍiva|
tathā tāṃ sa diteḥ putro jagrāha ruṣitānanaḥ|
uvāca caiva saṃrabdhastāṃ devīṃ bhayavihvalām|| 95.12||
tavāhaṃ vasudhe bhartā brahmaṇā prakṛtaḥ śubhe|
mānyaṃ patiṃ tvam icchethā rakṣikṣye 'ahaṃ tato hi te|| 95.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato rasātalaṃ gatvā svapurasya samīpataḥ|
babaddha nāgapāśaistāṃ duṣṭām iva yathāṅganām|| 95.14||
tato 'acalena daityendraḥ śaṃkhena sumahābalaḥ|
ārtāṃ rurodha duṣṭaśca kandarām iva vīryavān|| 95.15||
tato 'asyā rakṣaṇe nityam udyuktān rakṣiṇo dadhau|
kiṃkarān nāma daityendrān sahasrāṇi caturdaśa|| 95.16||
sa tathā tadvidhāyaiva daityendrastuṣṭimān babhau|
kṛṣībala iva kṣetraṃ suniṣpannaṃ samīkṣya ca|| 95.17||
kṛtakṛtyo 'aham ityeva buddhiṃ cakre sa pārthivaḥ|
saṃyujya svasutaṃ jyeṣṭhaṃ dāraiḥ sādhurivātmavān|| 95.18||
antaraṃ na ca tasyānyaḥ kaścit prāpnoti suvrata|
svasahāyasya viprasya yathā dambhena vartataḥ|| 95.19||
yajadhvaṃ dānavāḥ sarve viprān pūjayateti ca|
devaṃ ca śūlinaṃ sarve namasyata punaḥ punaḥ|| 95.20||
dharmam eva niṣevadhvam iti so 'ajñāpayat tadā|
na tasyā dhārmikaḥ kaściddaityo vā dānavo 'api vā|| 95.21||
rājye 'abhavaddurācārastasmin rājyaṃ praśāsati|
svayam eva sa vāyuśca candramāḥ sūrya eva ca|| 95.22||
abhavadvyāsa lokeṣu tapobalasamanvitaḥ|
oṣadhyaḥ svayam udbhūtāstasmin rājani śāsati|| 95.23||
vinā kṛṣṭiṃ sambhavanti sarvalokasya sādhikāḥ|
sa eva tāḥ samādāya kṣaraṃ nayati daityarāṭ|| 95.24||
sa evāmardayaccāpi nināya ca punargṛhān|
sa eva daṇḍiko 'abhūcca daṇḍaścaiva sa eva hi|| 95.25||
sa eva yogāt sarvatra caurādrakṣati nityadā|
na tasya vyādhitaḥ kaścinmriyate vāpi kaścana|| 95.26||
paradāraprasakto vā piśuno vāpi karhicit|
hiṃsakā na ca tasyāsan na cāpyadhārmikāḥ kvacit|| 95.27||
palvalāni taḍāgāni saritprasravaṇāni ca|
vinā vṛṣṭyā bhavantyete sarvatraiva ca susthitam|| 95.28||
na santi tasya rakṣāṃsi na piśācāśca hiṃsriṇaḥ|
ītayaśca na santyasya na dvandvāni ca kānicit|| 95.29||
na juhvate tadā vahniṃ viprāstasmiṃstu rājani|
nādhīyate yajante vā ekavarṇam abhūt tadā|| 95.30||
bhṛgavo ye 'abhavan viprā dānavānāṃ mudāvahāḥ|
adhīyate yajante ca evaṃ te vyāsa sarvaśaḥ|| 95.31||
hṛṣṭapuṣṭam abhūt sarvaṃ vyādhiduḥkhavivarjitam|
varṇāśramaparityaktaṃ sarvalokasamaṃ jagat|| 95.32||
tannṛtyagītotsavanityayuktaṃ sukhaprasuptaṃ ratikāryayuktam|
jagadbabhau rājani daityadeve hiraṇyanetre ditinandaneti|| 95.33||
|| iti skandapurāṇe hiraṇyākṣarājyavarṇano nāma
pañcanavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 95 ||

ṣaṇnavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
tathā rājani daityendre trailokyādhipatau śubhe|
dharaṇyāṃ caiva baddhāyāṃ sukhitāsu prajāsu ca|| 96.1||
sthānebhyaścyāvitā devā hyapratiṣṭhā mahābalāḥ|
kim akurvata duḥkhārttā etanme śaṃsa sarvaśaḥ|| 96.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇuṣva dharma (?) devānām avasthā yā babhūva ha|
yadakurvata duḥkhārttāstatra sarve yathākramam|| 96.3||
havyavāho 'agnirabhavaddevānāṃ bhāgavardhanaḥ|
taṃ nirasya tadā daityo vahnim anyaṃ cakāra ha|| 96.4||
tasmin karmaṇi viprendra mantrāstadanuhābhavan|
daityadānavabhāgānāṃ vaktāraḥ śubhasādhakāḥ|| 96.5||
tato yajñaḥ svayaṃ daityānupatasthe mahātmanaḥ|
yajñe gate ca daityendrād devāḥ sarve mṛtā iva|| 96.6||
abhavannaṣṭasaṃjñāśca mandavīryaparākramāḥ|
niḥśrīkāśca nirudyogā nirākrandāḥ samutsukāḥ|| 96.7||
mantradagdhā yathā sarpā vajrapiṣṭā yathācalāḥ|
garutmatābhisandaṣṭāḥ pannagā iva nirviṣāḥ|| 96.8||
vihīnādbhiryathā vṛkṣā bāndhavairvāpi yoṣitaḥ|
tathā te daivatā vyāsa hṛtarājyā hṛtaśriyaḥ|| 96.9||
cintayanti hṛdā caiva śuṣyanti vilapanti ca|
atha devaḥ svayambhūstāñjñātvā devāṃstathāvidhān|| 96.10||
vimānenārkavarṇena provācedaṃ pitāmahaḥ|
bho devā naṣṭasaṃjñā stha kimarthaṃ duḥkhitā bhṛśam|
tapoyogabalaṃ vo 'adya dadāmi surapuṅgavāḥ|| 96.11||
yūyaṃ lokasya kartāro hartāraścaiva sarvaśaḥ|
na yuktaṃ bhavatām etat klībavat sthātum adya vai|| 96.12||
svīyaṃ yogaṃ madīyaṃ ca tyaktvā duḥkhaṃ mahābalāḥ|
pratipadyata mā śoke svayaṃ devāḥ pravartata|| 96.13||
na tamo bhāskarādyuktaṃ na somāduṣṇatā yathā|
nāgneryathā tuṣāro nāmṛtaṃ bhujagādiva|| 96.14||
nāsādhoḥ sādhubhāvaśca na kulīnādaśobhanam|
nādharmo niyamebhyaśca na devebhyaśca durmatiḥ|| 96.15||
tathā na yuktaṃ yuṣmākam idaṃ devā mahātmanām|
āpatsu na viṣīdanti ye kecit tejasā sthitāḥ|| 96.16||
te yūyam āpadaṃ prāpya na śokaṃ kartum arhatha|
mā bhavanto 'avasīdantu rājyaṃ bhūyo bhaviṣyati|| 96.17||
mahāyogabalopeto hiraṇyākṣo 'adya devatāḥ|
aśakyo hantum alpena tejasā ditinandanaḥ|| 96.18||
pratīkṣanti bhavanto 'asya tapasaḥ kṣayam avyayāḥ|
kṣīṇe tapasi daityendraṃ yuddhe viṣṇurvadhiṣyati|| 96.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evaṃ brahmaṇā proktā labdhayogāḥ sureśvarāḥ|
praṇamya sarvabhūtānāṃ sraṣṭāram idam abruvan|| 96.20||
hṛtāni no mahāyogasthānāni ditinandanaiḥ|
kva tiṣṭhāma vayaṃ brūhi diśa naḥ sthānam avyayam|| 96.21||
brahmovāca|
hṛtāni sarvasthānāni yuṣmākaṃ viditaṃ ca me|
śṛṇudhvaṃ yatra vastavyaṃ yuṣmābhiryogamāyayā|| 96.22||
yūyaṃ sarve śarīreṣu yogādviśata sattamāḥ|
prajānāṃ sarvato devāstato vṛttim avāpsyatha|| 96.23||
teṣām aśitapītaiśca saṃskāraiśca pṛthagvidhaiḥ|
pṛthivī nāgabaddhāpi yuṣmān āpyāyayiṣyati|| 96.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā devena devāḥ sarve savāsavāḥ|
tathā cakruryathovāca brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|| 96.25||
te 'avartayanta satataṃ tatrasthāḥ surasattamāḥ|
caturyugam upāsanto lokadhāturmate sthitāḥ|| 96.26||
atha yogāddhiraṇyākṣaḥ prajāsu samavasthitān|
surānapaśyadyogātmā cukrodha ca sa tān prati|| 96.27||
yasmin yasminnapaśyacca suraṃ sa samavasthitam|
avadhīt taṃ tam abhyetya tadā dānavasattamaḥ|| 96.28||
ahaṃ prajāḥ sadodyukto rakṣāmi satataṃ bhayāt|
mamaiva tā durācārā vidviṣo vardhayantyuta|| 96.29||
kṛtaghnāḥ svāmighātinyo duṣpūrā duṣṭacetasaḥ|
mama śatrūnimā duṣṭānannapānādibhiḥ sadā|| 96.30||
āpyāyayanti durvṛttā daṇḍārhā me tatastu tāḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 96.31||
palvalāni taḍāgāni nadīḥ prasravaṇāni ca|
sarvāṇyeva tadā yogādaśoṣayata dānavaḥ|| 96.32||
oṣadhyo 'akṛṣṭapacyāśca yā hi āsaṃstasya suvrata|
vyanāśayat sa tāścāpi vṛkṣavallīrapothayat|| 96.33||
tannaṣṭavṛkṣakṣupavallipallavaṃ tṛṇauṣadhīprasravaṇodakāśayam|
sarittaḍāgāvaṭaśuṣkapallavaṃ jagadbabhau kacchapapṛṣṭhasannibham|| 96.34|
praṇaṣṭavarṇāśramadharmasaṃyamaṃ vinaṣṭaghoṣavrajapakṣimānuṣam|
dvipāśvapattyādigaṇairvināditaṃ yugāntakālāgnim udagravajjagat|| 96.35||
|| iti skandapurāṇe brahmaṇo vākyaṃ nāma
ṣaṇnavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 96 ||

saptanavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tathābhūtaṃ jagaddṛṣṭvā devāste duḥkhapīḍitāḥ|
vairājaṃ lokam āsādya bhūyo 'apaśyan pitāmaham|| 97.1||
te sarve samupāgamya praṇamya ca punaḥ punaḥ|
ūcuste karma daityasya sarvama eva suduḥkhitāḥ|| 97.2||
nivedya ca punardevam ūcuste lokakāraṇam|
bhagavan hṛtarājyāśca durbalāśca tathā vibho|| 97.3||
asamarthā vayaṃ tasya sthātuṃ daityasya saṃyuge|
na ca sthānaṃ prapaśyāmastatra tiṣṭhāma vijvarāḥ|| 97.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tadvacanamśrutvā bhītānāṃ tridivaukasām|
uvāca bhagavān brahmā sarvāneva divaukasaḥ|| 97.5||
na bhetavyaṃ surāstasya yoginaḥ sumahātmanaḥ|
samāptaṃ tapasaḥ sarvaṃ phalaṃ daityasya tasya tat|| 97.6||
kālastasyābhisamprāpto jīvitāntakaraḥ surāḥ|
tasmāt sarve mayā sārdhaṃ yāta viṣṇuṃ prayācata|| 97.7||
bhavanto nirbalā hyadya aśaktāstasya bādhane|
viṣṇuḥ śaktaḥ sa taṃ daityaṃ jīvitāccyāvayiṣyati|| 97.8||
pūrvaṃ hi jāte tasmiṃstu vāguvācāśarīriṇī|
nāyaṃ vadhyo manuṣyasya na devasya kathaṃcana|| 97.9||
nāpi tiryakṣu jātasya na bhūmau na ca tejasi|
nākāśe nāpi lokeṣu mahātmāyaṃ bhaviṣyati|| 97.10||
sa eṣa devā daityeśo mahātmā dhārmikastadā|
avadhyaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ vadhyo duḥkhādbhaviṣyati|| 97.11||
vārāhaṃ rūpam āsthāya na daivaṃ nāpi mānuṣam|
na ca tiryakṣu tajjātaṃ naravārāham asti vai|| 97.12||
pātāle ca praviśyaiva nāsau bhūrnāpi khaṃ hi tat|
na tejo nāpi loko 'asau sarvato muktam eva tat|| 97.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste hṛṣitāḥ sarve praṇamya ca pitāmaham|
ūcurgacchāma deveśa kālo 'atikramate hi naḥ|| 97.14||
tataste sarva evaitya śvetaṃ parvatasattamam|
viṣṇuṃ sahiṣṇuṃ jiṣṇuṃ ca dānavāyutamardanam|| 97.15||
astuvan vāgbhiriṣṭābhiḥ praṇamya bahumānataḥ|
namaḥ sarvaripughnāya dānavāntakarāya ca|| 97.16||
namo 'ajitāya devāya vaikuṇṭhāya mahātmane|
namo nirdhūtarajase namaḥ satyāya caiva hi|| 97.17||
namaḥ sādhyāya devāya namo dhāmne suvedhase|
namo yamāya devāya jayāya ca namo namaḥ|| 97.18||
namaścāditiputrāya naranārāyaṇāya ca|
namaḥ sumataye caiva namaścaivāstu viṣṇave|| 97.19||
namo vāmanarūpāya kṛṣṇadvaipāyanāya ca|
namo rāmāya rāmāya datātreyāya vai namaḥ|| 97.20||
namaste narasiṃhāya dhātre caiva namo namaḥ|
namaḥ sādhyāya vedāya cakriṇe vai namo namaḥ|| 97.21||
namaḥ śakunihantre ca namo dāmodarāya ca|
salile tapyamānāya nāgaśayyāpriyāya ca|| 97.22||
namaḥ kapilarūpāya mahate puruṣāya ca|
namo jīmūtarūpāya mahādevapriyāya ca|| 97.23||
namo rudrārdharūpāya tathomārūpiṇe namaḥ|
cakramudgarahastāya maheśvaragaṇāya ca|| 97.24||
śipiviṣṭāya ca sadā namaḥ śrīvatsadhāriṇe|
dhundhumārāya śūrāya madhukaiṭabhaghātine|| 97.25||
caturbhujāya kṛṣṇāya ratnakaustubhadhāriṇe|
trivikramaviyatsthāya pītavāsaḥsuvāsase|| 97.26||
namaḥ puruṣaghātāya gadākhaḍgogradhāriṇe|
yogine yajamānāya bhṛgupatnīpramāthine|| 97.27||
vṛṣarūpāya satatam ādityānāṃ varāya ca|
cekitānāya dāntāya śauriṇe vṛṣṇibandhave|| 97.28||
murāśvagrīvanāśāya tathaivāsurasūdine|
namaste śārṅgadhanuṣe saubhaśālvavighātnie|| 97.29||
namaste padmanābhāya brahmadehapraveśine|
namo jayāya śarvāya rudradattavarāya ca|| 97.30||
namaḥ sarveśvarāyaiva naṣṭadharmapravartine|
puruṣāya vareṇyāya namaste śatabāhave|| 97.31||
tava prasādāt kṛcchraṃ vai tarāmaḥ puruṣottama|
hṛtarājyā vayaṃ sarve na tvaṃ vetsi mahābhuja|
hiraṇyākṣeṇa vaikuṇṭhaṃ taṃ nāśaya mahābhuja|| 97.32||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya idaṃ vaiṣṇavaṃ stotraṃ bhaktyā paramayā yutaḥ|
kīrtayet satataṃ martyaḥ sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 97.33||
mṛtaśca sarvalokeṣu varṣakoṭicaturdaśa|
pūjitaḥ sarvadevaiśca modate nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 97.34||
kīrtayatyeva ya imaṃ prāṇibhyo vipramucyate|
sa mṛtyulokam aprāpya carate duḥkhavarjitaḥ|| 97.35||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
uvāca suraśārdūlānidaṃ sampūjayan sadā|| 97.36||
itaḥ sa daityo durbuddhirdevān dveṣṭi sahāyavān|
kriyatāṃ martyarūpaṃ me vārāhaṃ māṃ vidhāryatām|| 97.37||
mahātmā sa ca daityendro balavān dhārmikaśca ha|
na ca śakyo mayaikena hantuṃ satyaṃ bravīmi vaḥ|| 97.38||
sarvadevamayaṃ rūpaṃ vārāhaṃ nandivardhanam|
tat samāsthāya hantāsmi daityendraṃ taṃ mahābalam|| 97.39||
tena rūpeṇa sarveṣām asmākaṃ devasattamāḥ|
brahmā brahmatvam āpannaḥ prasthātā yama ityapi|| 97.40||
udgātā tatra varuṇo hiraṇyākṣastataḥ paśuḥ|
śamitāhaṃ suraśreṣṭhā yaśastasya mahābalaḥ|| 97.41||
adya paśyantu bhūtāni mama tasyaiva cobhayoḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 97.42||
araṇye vāsitāhetormattayorgajayoriva|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā garjitaṃ ca mahātmanaḥ|| 97.43||
harṣotphullekṣaṇāḥ sarve nirīkṣantaḥ parasparam|
menire hata ityeva daityendraṃ sumahābalam|| 97.44||
teṣāṃ tadutphullakuśeśayaprabhaṃ vakrekṣaṇaṃ cārutarāvabhāsakam|
hataḥ sa daityo narasiṃharūpiṇā yathā purā tasya gururmahābalaḥ|| 97.45||
|| iti skandapurāṇe hiraṇyākṣavadhopāyo nāma
saptanavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 97.97||

aṣṭanavatitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha te suraśārdūlāstasya rūpaṃ pracakrire|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
saptalokamayaṃ tasya śarīraṃ cakrurīśvarāḥ|| 98.1||
asthīni parvatāḥ sarve nadyo nāḍyaśca tasya tu|
rudhiraṃ cābdhayaḥ sapta kaphapittānilā guṇāḥ|| 98.2||
purīṣaṃ cāpyoṣadhayo dharmo retaḥ kṛto 'asya tu|
mūtraṃ tasyābhavan meghā vāyavaḥ sapta koṣṭhagāḥ|| 98.3||
śirastasyābhavan sādhyā rudro mūrdhānam āsthitaḥ (?)|
lalāṭe tasya dharmo 'abhūnnāsikā vāyurātmavān|| 98.4||
sūryācandramasau netre śrotre tasya diśo 'abhavan|
bhruvostasyābhavan prāṇā ahorātraṃ ca pakṣamaṇī|| 98.5||
āsyaṃ tasyāgnirabhavadvaḍavā mukhasaṃsthitā|
oṣṭhe 'abhūdantarikṣaṃ ca dantāśca bhujagābhavan|| 98.6||
catvāryastrāṇi daṃṣṭrāśca kṛtāni sumahānti vai|
astraṃ pāśupataṃ pūrvaṃ dvitīyaṃ cakram eva ca|| 98.7||
brahmadaṇḍaṃ tṛtīyaṃ ca caturthaṃ brahmaṇaḥ śiraḥ|
grīvā tasyābhavat somo rudraḥ skandhe ca saṃsthitaḥ|| 98.8||
gaṇḍe cāpi tathādityā hastau rudraiśca nirmitau|
aṅgulyastasya kīrtiśca lakṣmīḥ siddhistathaiva ca|| 98.9||
-- -- -- --pravṛttiśca nakhāścāstrāṇi sarvaśaḥ|
yamadaṇḍaḥ kāladaṇḍo mṛtyudaṇḍastathaiva ca|| 98.10||
rudradaṇḍaśca catvāro bāhupādāḥ kṛtāḥ prabhoḥ|
sādhyā devā urastasya hṛdayaṃ soma ityapi|| 98.11||
udaraṃ tasya bhūtāni mahānti ṛṣisattama|
nābhistasyābhavanmātā aditirbrahmasattama|| 98.12||
śiśnaṃ prajāpatistasya mitro 'apāne 'abhavat sthitaḥ|
vasavastasya pārśveṣu tathā dharmaśca pṛṣṭhataḥ|| 98.13||
mṛtyuḥ kālo yamaścaiva hastapādatalāśritāḥ|
aśvinau tasya lāṅgūlaṃ pitaraḥ sandhiṣu sthitāḥ|| 98.14||
niyatiḥ kālapāśaśca kṛtāntakalahāvapi|
vyādhayaścāpi ye keciddṛṣṭiṃ tasya samāśritāḥ|| 98.15||
yakṣāśca rākṣasāścaiva gandharvāḥ pannagaiḥ saha|
sarva tvacaṃ samāśritya saṃhatāḥ samavasthitāḥ|| 98.16||
tathā sarvāṇi chandāṃsi vedā iṣṭaya eva ca|
romakūpeṣu sarvāṇi tāni tasthuḥ pṛthak pṛthak|| 98.17||
dānāni niyamāścaiva yamāḥ sarvāśca mātaraḥ|
sthānābhimānino devāḥ paśavaḥ pakṣaṇaśca ha|| 98.18||
sarve romāṇi tasyāsan varāhasya mahātmanaḥ|
aṅgulyastasya pādābhyāṃ veśvedevābhavaṃstathā|| 98.19||
bhṛgavo 'aṅgirasaścaiva devāstasyābhavaṃstadā|
romāntareṣu ṛṣayaḥ sarveṣvaṅgeṣu saṃsthitāḥ|| 98.20||
evaṃ samabhavadvyāsa varāho nandivardhanasḥ|
sas bhāti tena rūpeṇa dyāṃ bhuvaṃ cāpi saṃspṛśan|| 98.21||
purā svayambhūrbhagavānuddhariṣyan mahīm imām|
sa reje tena rūpeṇa dīptimān madhusūdanaḥ|| 98.22||
niśāyāṃ sampradīpto hi himavāniva parvataḥ|
tatastam ṛṣayaḥ sarve tapasā mahatā tadā|| 98.23||
svena svenābhisamprāpya tejastasyābhyadīpayan|
sa viṣṇustejasā teṣām ṛṣīṇāṃ paramaujasām|| 98.24||
samprajajvāla kālānte yuhāntāgnirivāparaḥ|
nādaṃ kṛtvā ca sumahaccālayāno mahītalam|| 98.25||
uvāca tānṛṣīn sarvān hanmi daityaṃ suradviṣam|
hatvā taṃ daityarājaṃ vai siṃhaṃ śarabharāḍiva|| 98.26||
mocayiṣye mahīṃ vignāṃ praviśyādya rasātalam|
svasthāne sthāpayitvā ca dattvā rājyaṃ divaukasām|
japadhvaṃ vijayāyādya śivāya ca rapodhanāḥ|| 98.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
uvāca balam ādhatsva daityo 'asau sumāhabalaḥ|| 98.28||
āsthāya yatnaṃ sumahadapramattaḥ sureśvara|
jahi taṃ daityarājaṃ vai kṛcchram etanmataṃ mama|| 98.29||
na tasya sadṛśo daityo hiraṇyakaśipuḥ purā|
mahābalo 'ayaṃ daityendrastapoyogasamanvitaḥ|| 98.30||
tato devastadā vyāsa bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|
suraiḥ sabrahmakaistatra ṛṣibhiśca tapodhanaiḥ|| 98.31||
uktaḥ praṇamya deveśo viṣṇum āpyāya prabho|
tejasā svena sarveśa yathā hanyāt suradviṣam|| 98.32||
bhagavānuvāca|
tasmin kāle sureśānāḥ sarve tejomayaṃ harim|
pravekṣyanti tato daityaṃ kṣipram eva nihaṃsyati|| 98.33||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato brahmā svayaṃ tasya rakṣāṃ cakre mahātmanaḥ|
yathāvat tāṃ nibodhādya vadanto me śucivrata|| 98.34||
brahmovāca|
rakṣantu tvāṃ vidhātā ca dhātā ca ṛṣisattama|
rudraḥ sraṣṭā ca sarveṣāṃ karmāṇi tava yudhyataḥ|| 98.35||
kapālī tālaketuśca gandhādhipatireva ca|
rasasyādhipatiścaiva sūkṣmarūpaśca rakṣatu|| 98.36||
sparśavettā ca yaḥ sūkṣmo nādavāṃśca mahāmanāḥ|
indriyādhipatiścaiva nīlalohita eva ca|| 98.37||
rakṣatu tvāṃ mahāyogī bījādhipatireva ca|
bījādhiṣṭhānamālaśca cetanāpatireva ca|| 98.38||
pravṛtteśca nivṛtteśca kālavettā ca yaḥ prabhuḥ|
dharmādharmagatiścaiva kartR̥ṇāṃ phaladaḥ prabhuḥ|| 98.39||
guṇānāṃ vṛttido yaśca anapekṣaśca karmasu|
niyamasya ca yaḥ kartā karmavettā ca karmaṇām|| 98.40||
vinā ca karaṇairyaśca karaṇārthaṃ pravartate|
sarvajñaḥ sarvago yaśca adhiṣṭhātā ca yaḥ svayam|| 98.41||
yena nādhiṣṭhitaṃ kiṃcit kathaṃcinnāpi vidyate|
sarvataḥpāṇipādāntaḥ sarvatokṣiśiromukhaḥ|
sarvataḥ śrutimāṃścaiva sarvatogatiravyayaḥ|| 98.42||
aiśvaryam akṣayaṃ yasya sahasrākṛtayastathā|
yaḥ sraṣṭā sarvabhūtānāṃ tattvanāṃ ca mahāyaśāḥ|| 98.43||
saṃsārasyāsya yaḥ kartā tathaiva ca nivartakaḥ|
yaṃ sāṃkhyā nābhijānanti yogino viditāgamāḥ|| 98.44||
tuṣṭayo jñātayo nityaṃ māyayā mohayan prajāḥ|
otaprotāni caitasmiṃstattvāni sumahātmani|| 98.45||
puruṣādīni sarvāṇi yo vyāptaśca na kenacit|
yam ajñātvā na mokṣo 'asti yena baddham idaṃ jagat|| 98.46||
yenāhaṃ sarvalokānāṃ kṛtaḥ pūrvaṃ prajāpatiḥ|
tvaṃ yajñaścaiva viṣṇuśca yena sṛṣṭāḥ purātana|| 98.47||
sa te balaṃ ca sumahadūrjaṃ tejaśca yacchatu|
akāmalabdhāṃ sarvatra smṛtiṃ cāstre mahāmanāḥ|| 98.48||
rakṣāṃ ca sarvago devo yudhyataste prayacchatu|
kṛtarakṣo mayā samyaggaccha daityaṃ vināśaya|| 98.49||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastaṃ stutibhirviprāstasya romāntarasthitāḥ|
astuvan vāgbhiriṣṭābhirdevāśca bahumānataḥ|| 98.50||
sarvāṇi ca jayeti ūcurbhūtāni vividhāni ca|
anāhatāstato vyomni devadundubhayaḥ śubhāḥ|| 98.51||
vinedustatra divyāśca varāho yatra so 'abhavat|
surabhīṇāṃ ca puṣpāṇāṃ varāhopari sarvataḥ|
vṛṣṭayaḥ peturatyarthaṃ devānāṃ harṣavardhanāḥ|| 98.52||
tataḥ siddhiriti procya kṛtvā rudrāya vai namaḥ|
japañjayāvahaṃ rudraṃ sa yayau varuṇālayam|| 98.53||
sa sevyamāno munibhistapodhanaistathā śakuntairbahubhirjayāvahaiḥ|
mṛgaiśca divyairbahubhiḥ pradakṣiṇairjayāya devaḥ prayayau mahārṇavam|| 98.54||
|| iti skandapurāṇe varāhasya
varuṇālayagamanaṃ nāmāṣṭanavatitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 98.98||

ekonaśatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa samprayāto dharmātmā nardamāno yathā ghanaḥ|
sarvalokamayo vedo varāho nandivardhanaḥ|| 99.1||
apaśyat sāgaraṃ caiva samprāpyātibalastadā|
nardamānaṃ yathā meghaṃ līyamānaṃ mṛgendravat|| 99.2||
nartakīm iva nṛtyantaṃ valgantaṃ caiva yodhavat|
maṇḍalairbahubhiścitraiścarantaṃ vasudhāṃ tathā|| 99.3||
niyuddhakuśalaṃ yadvadgadāyuddhaviśāradam|
tadā tadbahudhā citram apaśyannandivardhanaḥ|| 99.4||
sa tam argheṇa deveśaṃ sarcalokamayaṃ vibhum|
pūjayāmāsa devāṃśca ṛṣayo ye ca saṃgatāḥ|| 99.5||
sa jayāya pragṛhyainam anumānya mahodadhim|
nivartya sarvabhūtāni praviveśa mahārṇavam|| 99.6||
vigāhamānaḥ sakrīḍam arṇavaṃ vibabhau vibhuḥ|
saraḥ sumahadāsādya yathā matto mahāgajaḥ|| 99.7||
sampraviśya sudūraṃ ca so 'adṛśyaḥ samapadyata|
bhūmilekhāvṛtaḥ sūryo yathā sampūrṇamaṇḍalaḥ|| 99.8||
tato 'antarjalam āviśya kṣobhayāṇo mahārṇavam|
jalacandrakavadvyāsa adṛśyata sa lokapaiḥ|| 99.9||
timintimiṅgilaṃ caiva timiṅgalagilānapi|
tathaiva tadgilānanyān gardabhān hastino 'api|| 99.10||
makarāṃścaiva śaṅkhāṃśca tathaivāśvamukhānapi|
tathā vai pakṣisaṃkāśān mānuṣānapi cāparān|| 99.11||
rathacakraprakārāṃśca siṃhavyāghramukhānapi|
śarabharkṣaviḍālāsyān matsyān bahuvidhāṃstathā|| 99.12||
bhrāmayan sumahātejā jagāma sumahābalaḥ|
kutūhalāt tam āviśya kecidāghrāya caiva hi|| 99.13||
daśanti matsyā dīptāsyāḥ śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|
sa pradakṣiṇam āvṛtya divyaṃ hayaśiraḥ śubham|| 99.14||
kṣaṇānmainākamadhyena gatvā bhogavatīm api|
varuṇasya purīṃ gatvā payonāthasya dhīmataḥ|| 99.15||
parjanyaṃ diggajaṃ prāpya kṛtvā cāpi pradakṣiṇam|
surabhīpuram āsādya gā dṛṣṭvā caiva suprabhāḥ|| 99.16||
yāḥ kṣaranti sadā vyāsa sudhām amṛtam eva ca|
kṣīrodaṃ tat saro divyaṃ phenapā yatra te dvijāḥ|| 99.17||
tasmin sarasi tat pītvā yaśomṛtasamaprabham|
pūjitaḥ phenapaiḥ samyak tāṃ rātriṃ tatra so 'avasat|| 99.18||
uṣitvā tatra so 'agacchat kaṅkasya puram avyayam|
vāsukeśca puraṃ prāpya takṣakasya ca dhīmataḥ|| 99.19||
tatra śeṣasya deveśo vindatāmaratām iti|
ramyāṃ manojñāṃ divyāṃ ca svargādapi ca tāṃ varām|| 99.20||
śrutvānataśca taṃ rājā argheṇa samapūjayat|
praṇamya bahumānācca upāmantrayadavyayaḥ|| 99.21||
taṃ pūjayānaṃ madhuhā prītyā paramayā yutaḥ|
uvāca lokakāryasya na vighnaṃ kartum arhasi|| 99.22||
mahat kāryam idaṃ deva kartavyaṃ tridivaukasām|
bhūyo vayaṃ tvayā sārdhaṃ kariṣyāma yadīcchasi|
mā ca kālo 'ayam udyukto daityasya na bhavediti|| 99.23||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato visṛjya taṃ nāgaṃ rasātalam upāgamat|
tatra sāgarapo daityaḥ suprabho 'antarjalecaraḥ|| 99.24||
apaśyat taṃ tadāyāntaṃ hiraṇyākṣapuraṃ prati|
gātreṣu devān sūkṣmāṃśca varāhasyānvavaikṣata|| 99.25||
tasmiṃstaccāsya rūpeṇa bhayānnainam upāgamat|
tejasā cāpi viṣṭabdho durātmā tasya so 'asuraḥ|| 99.26||
āvedayiṣyaṃstasmai hi hiraṇyākṣāya satvaram|
cakre vegaṃ pratipuraṃ varāhasya tadāgrataḥ|| 99.27||
sa yātukāmo ditijādhirājaṃ varāharūpaṃ tam anantam antakam|
jagāma daityāya sa jīvitāntaṃ yathānilaḥ pradyutadānamālyavān|| 99.28||
|| iti skandapurāṇe varāhasya
sāgarapraveśo nāmaikonaśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 99.99||

skandapurana100
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasmin bhaye samāpanne vināśabhayasūcakaḥ|
hiraṇyākṣapure ghorāstpātā hyabhavan tadā|| 100.1||
aṭṭālakā viśīryante devatāścāhasanniva|
śivā nadanti daityānāṃ gṛheṣu ca sabhāsu ca|| 100.2||
akasmāccābhavat tatra paurāṇāṃ bhairavo ravaḥ|
pādapāśca vinā vātaṃ patantyunmūlitā bhuvi|
bhāskaraśca kabandhābho yuddhaṃ cāpyatra dṛśyate|| 100.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
etānyanyāni ca tadā nimittāni mahānti ca|
saṃlakṣya rājā daityānām asurānidam abravīt|| 100.4||
nimittānyabhilakṣyante mahāntyasurapuṃgavāḥ|
naiva tānyanimittāni dṛśyate ca bhayaṃ mahat|| 100.5||
hṛtarājyāśca deveśā na te sthāsyanti niṣkriyāḥ|
nūnaṃ te kiṃcidāśritya kurvanti samaraṃ prati|| 100.6||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā prahlādo 'asurasattamaḥ|
praṇamya pitaraṃ samyagidaṃ vacanam abravit|| 100.7||
prahlāda uvāca|
suto 'ahaṃ tava daityendra pitā tvaṃ mama dharmataḥ|
na tavāsmadvidhairbuddhiradheyā daityasattama|| 100.8||
tathāpi tu vayaṃ prītyā icchanto rājyam akṣayam|
vakṣyāmo bālabhāvena tanna saṃsmartum arhasi|| 100.9||
adya rātrau mayā svapne dṛṣṭo 'asau nararūpavān|
varāharūpaṃ saṃgatya bhavantaṃ nigṛhītavān|
na tathā tadyathā syāddhi tathā tvaṃ samyagācara|| 100.10||
hiraṇyākṣa uvāca|
evam etanna saṃdeho bhavān yaddharmatastadā|
dṛṣṭavāṃstadyathātattvam evam etanna saṃśayaḥ|| 100.11||
aham adya gataḥ svapne tryambakasya niveśāne|
tataḥ sa mām idaṃ prāha bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|| 100.12||
etāvadbhavato daitya rājyam indratvam eva ca|
yacchemāṃ tvaṃ priyāṃ putra sahayakṣāya suprabhām|| 100.13||
kṣipram etāṃ prayacchādya mukuṭaṃ hāram eva ca|
keyūrāṅgadakaṃ caiva khaḍgaṃ rucakam eva ca|| 100.14||
kaṭake śāsanaṃ caiva dukūlaṃ ca tathotarīm|
anicchato me saṃgṛhya śakrasya pradadau tadā|| 100.15||
tato māma bhagavān āha matsamīpe tvayā sadā|
kalyaṃ prabhṛti vastavyaṃ kiṃ te rājyena daityapa|| 100.16||
yadetaddhi mayā dṛṣṭaṃ na tanmithyā bhaviṣyati|
sarvathā nāsti daityānāṃ mayaikena bhavaṃ tviha|| 100.17||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā daityāḥ sarve tadābruvan|
mithyaitat svapnagatayo mithyā rājan prakīrtitāḥ|| 100.18||
andhakaḥ sahito 'asmābhiryotsyate daivataiḥ saha|
yo 'avadhyaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ balavānajitaśca ha|| 100.19||
tam āśritya vayaṃ sarve yotsyāmo vijvarāḥ sukham|
mā yudhyatu bhavān sārdhaṃ suraiḥ surabalārdana|| 100.20||
tvayi prāṇāḥ sthitāḥ sarve daityānāṃ dānavaiḥ saha|
tvayi jīvati jīvāmastvaṃ cennāsi kuto vayam|
tyaktvā vādya puraṃ sarve praviśāma mahodadhim|| 100.21||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā hirāṇyākṣo mahāsuraḥ|
prahasya tānidaṃ samyaguvāca vadatāṃ varaḥ|| 100.22||
sraṣṭā yaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ dātā hartā tathaiva ca|
vihitaṃ tena yat pūrvaṃ tat kuryāt ko 'anyathā punaḥ|| 100.23||
yadi mṛtyuravaśyaṃ me vihitastena dānavāḥ|
ayudhyamānam āsīnam etyāsau mā vadhiṣyati|| 100.24||
vīkṣadhvaṃ tanmama sthānaṃ sarva evāsurottamāḥ|
yatra tiṣṭhantam abhyetya na mā mṛtyurnayiṣyati|| 100.25||
atha vā naiva mṛtyurme vihitastena dānavāḥ|
yudhyamānaṃ yathā pūrvaṃ naiva māṃ sa nayiṣyati|| 100.26||
mādṛśaḥ katham evaitat kuryāt sadbhirvigarhitam|
bāle mṛtyuṃ samāveśya tataścātmāntarekṣaṇam|| 100.27||
raṇe ripūṇāṃ kadanaṃ kṛtvaikaścāpyanekaśaḥ|
pṛṣṭhaṃ dadyāt punasteṣāṃ mādṛśo dānaveśvarāḥ|| 100.28||
vipracittiruvāca|
devā hyanekaśaḥ sarve jitā naṣṭāśca sarvaśaḥ|
punaścāyānti na yathā tathā sarve yatāmahe|| 100.29||
hiraṇyākṣa uvāca|
amaraṃ devatā jñātvā svam ātmānaṃ sudurlabham|
jīvantaḥ sucireṇāpi bhūyo lapsyāmahe vayam|| 100.30||
rājyam evaṃ vijānanto vipalāyanti nityaśaḥ|
asmākam amaratvaṃ tu naivāstyasurasattamāḥ|| 100.31||
naṣṭānām apyato 'asmākaṃ jīvitāśā na vidyate|
tasyām asatyāṃ paśyāma yat prāptaṃ taddhi no varam|| 100.32||
mā kṛthā nāśane buddhiṃ yuddhe buddhiḥ sthitā mama|
suyuddhena raṇe prāṇā yāntu mā klībavaddhi naḥ|| 100.33||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣām evaṃ tu vadatāṃ sabhāyāṃ suravidviṣām|
vegasvāsābhisaṃrabdho dānavaḥ pratyadṛśyata|| 100.34||
samyak saṃtrāsita iva mṛgarājena nirjane|
karīva siṃhapādena garuḍeneva pannagaḥ|| 100.35||
tadā sa baddhamuṣṭiśca diśaḥ sarvā vilokayan|
vegena niḥśvasan gatvā dvāri dvāḥstham abhāṣata|| 100.36||
dānava uvāca|
āvedaya sabhāpāla rājñe prāpto 'analaḥ svayam|
sāgarārakṣikaḥ kṣipram akālaṃ śīghram ucyate|| 100.37||
tataḥ prahasya taṃ dvāḥsthaḥ sabhāpālo 'abhibhāṣya tam|
uvāca mā bhīrbhavatu kuto bhīste mahāsura|| 100.38||
neha siṃho 'asti coro vā nānyaḥ śvāpada ityapi|
na gāvaḥ paśavo 'anye vā bhayaṃ tyaja samāśvasa|| 100.39||
sa tathā tena samprokto 'aśāntaścāsurasattamaḥ|
kruddhaḥ śabdaṃ tadā cakre mahāntaṃ nādayan diśaḥ|| 100.40||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
te 'abhigamya tadā vyāsa rājānaṃ dānaveśvaram|
ūcureṣa kim apyadya dṛṣṭaṃ kathayate 'asuraḥ|| 100.41||
sa rājan samyagāśvāsya daityam enaṃ mahāyaśaḥ|
dānavānāṃ hitārthāya pṛcchasva ditinandana|| 100.42||
teṣāṃ sa rājā viprendra dānavānāṃ mahābalaḥ|
śrutvā taṃ dānavaṃ vyāsa idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 100.43||
bhayaṃ na śaknute daitya matsamīpe 'abhivartitum|
brūhi sarvaṃ yathādṛṣṭaṃ samāśvasya tathātatham|| 100.44||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa dānavo vyāsa rājānaṃ vigatajvaraḥ|
praṇamya prā~calirvākyam idaṃ samyaguvāca ha|| 100.45||
nityaṃ jayatu no rājā dānavānāṃ sukhāvahaḥ|
naśyantu vidviṣaḥ sarve ye 'asmākam ahitāvahāḥ|| 100.46||
ahaṃ tavājñayā sarvaṃ vicarāmi dine dine|
sāgarāntaṃ mahārāja puruṣaiḥ saha saṃgataḥ|| 100.47||
so 'adya paśyāmyahaṃ tatra varāhaṃ daityapuṃgava|
meruśṛṅgapratīkāśaṃ jvalantam iva pāvakam|| 100.48||
tasya gāteṣu dṛśyante sūkṣmarūpadharāḥ sthitāḥ|
sarve surā mahārāja ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|| 100.49||
mahābalastvaṃ rājendra devānāṃ bhayadaḥ sadā|
tvatto 'api sumahān bhīmastādṛṅnaiveha vidyate|| 100.50||
na dṛṣṭo na śruto vāpi vapuṣā daityapuṃgava|
ahaṃ tenāhato dṛṣṭyā nyapataṃ bhūtale bhṛśam|| 100.51||
srastahārāmbaro bhītaḥ kuliśeneva tāḍitaḥ|
ye mamānucarāścāsan dānavā bhīmavikramāḥ|| 100.52||
te sarve tasya vegena patitā gatajīvitāḥ|
sa eṣo 'abhyeti rājendra tavaiva nagaraṃ prati|| 100.53||
cālayan vasudhāṃ sarvāṃ kṣobhayan sāgarāṃstathā|
jalecarāṃśca daityendra jīvitairviprayojayan|| 100.54||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā prahlādo 'asurasattamaḥ|
uvāca daityarājānam idaṃ vacanam arthavat|| 100.55||
prahlāda uvāca|
yādṛśaṃ tadvarāhasya tasya rūpaṃ mayā śrutam|
sarvadevamayaṃ rājan varāho 'aprākṛto mataḥ|| 100.56||
tasmāt tvayā vidhātavyaṃ yathā no na sa mohayet|
viniścitya ca daityendra mā ciraṃ tadvidhīyatām|| 100.57||
suvyaktaṃ brahmaṇā tasya cakralāṅgaladhāriṇas|
sarvadevamayaṃ rūpaṃ vārāham idam īhitam|| 100.58||
bhavānavadhyaḥ sarveṣāṃ devānāṃ dānaveśvara|
aśaktaistairiyaṃ māyā sṛṣṭā vai na tadanyathā|| 100.59||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca daityān danujānidaṃ vacanam arthavat|| 100.60||
hiraṇyākṣa uvāca|
yadyeṣa bhrātṛhantā me ihāyāti durātmavān|
pūrṇaḥ syādadya sucirādyo me hṛdi manorathaḥ|| 100.61||
adyāhaṃ taṃ durātmānaṃ bhrātṛhantāram āhave|
chittvā chittvā kariṣyāmi baliṃ paśupateḥ śubham|| 100.62||
adya tasya vicitrākṣaṃ śiraḥ kāyāt sakuṇḍalam|
utkṛtya daityā dāsyāmi rudrāya paramātmane|| 100.63||
mayā nāsāditaḥ pūrvaṃ tasmin yuddhe sa keśavaḥ|
adyāhaṃ taṃ samāsādya neṣyāmi yamasādanam|| 100.64||
atha tasmin hate sarve nirāśā bhayavihvalāḥ|
mamaivākāryatāṃ gatvā devā yāsyanti dāsatām|| 100.65||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa dānavāñchūrān daityāṃśca sumahābalān|
uvāca nāmnā vikhyātān kiṃkarān nāma dānavān|| 100.66||
daśa tāni sahasrāṇi gacchadhvaṃ taṃ mahābalāḥ|
jānīta ko 'ayam ityevaṃ tato yāsyāmyahaṃ svayam|| 100.67||
te tathoktā mahāmāyā hṛṣṭāḥ sarve vinirgatāḥ|
baddhagodhāṅgulitrāṇāḥ saṃnaddhāstu padātayaḥ|| 100.68||
te hemacitrāmbarahārasūtrā mahābalā dānavadaityaputrāḥ|
vinādayanto bahudhātikopitā yathaiva nāgāḥ saviṣā viniryayuḥ|| 100.69||
iti skandapurāṇe kiṃkarādeśanaṃ nāma śatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 100.100||

skandapurana101
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te 'abhinirgatya vegena daṃśitā daityadānavāḥ|
varāhaṃ prati saṃjagmurmṛgāḥ siṃham ivāturāḥ|| 101.1||
te varāhadṛśā tena nīyamānāsureśvarāḥ|
ābhānti vyāsa saṃnaddhāḥ prokṣitāḥ paśavo yathā|| 101.2||
tān nihatya kṛtāntena mṛtyunā cāvapāśitān|
nināya sa tadā daityān paśūniva yathā naraḥ|| 101.3||
gatvā te yojanānyaṣṭau uttīrṇaṃ sāgarāmbhasaḥ|
varāhaṃ dadṛśuḥ sarve siṃhaṃ kṣudramṛgā iva|| 101.4||
te muhūrtaṃ nirīkṣyaiva paribabhruḥ samantataḥ|
visphārayantaścāpāni saṃkruddhā daityadānavāḥ|| 101.5||
tān āpatata evātha nirīkṣya sa samantataḥ|
varāhendrastadā daityān prāhedaṃ sumahābalaḥ|| 101.6||
varāhsa uvāca|
kiṃ mā yūyaṃ diteḥ putrā abhidravatha sarvaśaḥ|
dūṣayāmi na vaḥ kiṃcidasuhṛnna ca vo hyaham|| 101.7||
athaivaṃvādinaṃ daityā varāhaṃ taṃ suvismitāḥ|
papracchuḥ parivāryaiva sarve ditisutāstadā|| 101.8||
kastvaṃ varāharūpīha tīrtvā sāgaram ūrjitam|
ihāgataḥ kimarthaṃ vā kva vā gantavyam ityuta|| 101.9||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā varāho 'asau mahāmanāḥ|
uvāca dānavān sarvāṃstadā jaladanisvanaḥ|| 101.10||
varāho 'ahaṃ yathā daityāstādṛgrūpaṃ ca paśyata|
pracārārtham imaṃ deśam āgato 'asmi na saṃśayaḥ|| 101.11||
hṛtabhāryo 'aham anyena vimanā daityapuṃgavāḥ|
paryaṭaṃstasya duṣṭasya cintayāmi parigraham|| 101.12||
dānavā ūcuḥ|
nāyaṃ pracāro yuṣmākaṃ daityānām ayam ālayaḥ|
anādṛtya kathaṃ daityānimaṃ deśam upāgataḥ|| 101.13||
vayaṃ tvādya vadhiṣyāmaḥ sarve mṛgakulādhama|
hatvā ca tvāṃ hi neṣyāmaḥ sarve daityeśvaraṃ prati|| 101.14||
tataste dānavāḥ sarve tam āyudhavarairbhṛśam|
nijaghnuḥ parvataṃ yadvat meghā vṛṣṭyā samuddhatāḥ|| 101.15||
balavān so 'api devātmā varāhaḥ sumahābalaḥ|
vadhyamāno 'api tān daityānidaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 101.16||
na hyatra bhavatāṃ kiṃcidalpam apyasurottamāḥ|
aparādhaṃ cakārāhaṃ na kariṣye karomi vā|| 101.17||
kimarthaṃ mā śitaiḥ śastrairghnata (?) sarve yathā param|
na hi vo vairam astīha na ca kāryaṃ mayā hi vaḥ|| 101.18||
atha māṃsena kṛtyaṃ vastato māṃ ghnata dānavāḥ|
yathā prāṇaṃ śitaiḥ śastrairyuṣmatto na ca me bhayam|| 101.19||
etau karau prasāryāhaṃ saṃsthito ditinandanāḥ|
yadā bhavantaḥ sthāsyanti tadā hantāsmi vaḥ sakṛt|| 101.20||
adya vetsyatha daiteyā mṛgāṇām iha yadbalam|
mattā yūyaṃ surāñjitvā taṃ madaṃ nāśayāmi vaḥ|| 101.21||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān vyāsa śakradhvajanibhau karau|
prasārya tasthāvudyañcau bhagavāniva śaṃkaraḥ|| 101.22||
te 'api tadvacanaṃ śrutvā dānavāḥ krodhamūrchitāḥ|
nijaghnurbhṛśam āyastā nānāśastrāstrapāṇayaḥ|| 101.23||
meghairiva mahāvāyurgarutmān bhujagairiva|
mṛgairiva yathā vyāghraḥ śaśairiva yathā hariḥ|| 101.24||
haviṣevānalo dīpto gajo gomāyubhiryathā|
tathā sa bhagavān vyāsa varāho nandivardhanaḥ|| 101.25||
tairadyamāno gaṇayan tasthāvacalasaṃnibhaḥ|
sa yadā taiḥ śaraiścaiva gadāmuśalapaṭṭiśaiḥ|| 101.26||
bhindipālairbhuśuṇḍībhiḥ karavālairayomukhaiḥ|
etaiścānyaiśca bahubhirvadhyamāno mṛgeśvaraḥ|
adṛśyo vibabhau sarve tadā te harṣitā bhṛśam|| 101.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ ninadatāṃ vyāsa varāho nandivardhanaḥ|
śastrakūṭādviniṣkramya śirāṃsi samapothayat|| 101.28||
karābhyāṃ caraṇābhyāṃ ca daṃṣṭrābhiśca vyadārayat|
tanmuktairāyudhaiścaiva cicchedānyān rarāsa sa|| 101.29||
te sarve karacaṇairvimuktaśastrairdaṃṣṭrābhirmukhadāritāstathaiva|
saṃkṣīṇā bahubhirivopabhujyamānā dravyāṇām iva nicayāḥ sadā mahāntaḥ|| 101.30||
iti skandapurāṇe kiṃkarayuddhe ekottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 101.101||

skandapurana102
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha tān nihatān sarvān varāheṇābhivīkṣya tu|
ekaḥ kṛcchrādvinirmukto hyaśamakaṃ puram āviśat|| 102.1||
sa gatvā tat sabhādvāram idaṃ vacanam abravīt|
muktakeśo rajodhvasto rudhireṇābhisamplutaḥ|| 102.2||
nivedayata bho daityā dānavendrāya dhīmate|
dvāḥstho nyavedayadrājñe preritaḥ sodyatāyudhaḥ|| 102.3||
ye te gatā mṛgendraṃ taṃ draṣṭuṃ hyasurasattamāḥ|
te hatāstena vikramya sarva eva diteḥ sutāḥ|| 102.4||
mā gāḥ pramādaṃ daityendra māvamaṃsthā mṛgeśvaram|
mā ca kālaṃ pratīkṣadhvaṃ mṛgaṃ taṃ mā vijānata|
mahānasau na saṃdeho jetuṃ śakyo na dānavaiḥ|| 102.5||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā hiraṇyākṣo mahāsuraḥ|
svayam evābhisaṃkruddha utpapāta tadāsanāt|| 102.6||
sendraketurivottasthau payoda iva connadan|
bhṛkuṭīdūṣitamukhaḥ sadhūmo 'agniriva jvalan|| 102.7||
athotthitaṃ tato daityā vipracittiśca dānavaḥ|
praṇamyocustadā daityam idaṃ ślakṣṇapadākṣaram|| 102.8||
tvaṃ rājā sarvadaityānāṃ bhūtānāṃ ca jayāvahaḥ|
tiṣṭhatsvasmāsu nodyantuṃ svayam eva tvam arhasi|| 102.9||
vayaṃ taṃ saha devaiśca ye ca tasyābhirakṣiṇaḥ|
hatvā māṃsaṃ mahārāja chittvā tasyānayāmahe|| 102.10||
ādityānāṃ sarudrāṇāṃ vasūnām aśvinorapi|
bhṛgūṇāṃ pitṛbhiḥ sārdhaṃ tathaivāṅgirasām api|| 102.11||
viśvedevāśca ye kecit sādhyā devāstathaiva ca|
yakṣāṇāṃ rākṣasānāṃ ca piśācānāṃ sahoragaiḥ|| 102.12||
gandharvapakṣiṇāṃ caiva manuṣyāṇāṃ ca dānava|
udyuktānāṃ samṛtyūnāṃ lokapālaiḥ sahaiva ca|| 102.13||
śaktā nivāraṇe daityā vadhe caiva durātmanām|
nigrahe ca yathākālaṃ svayaṃ mā tvam ito gamaḥ|| 102.14||
hatam asmābhirudyuktaiḥ paśyādya ditinandana|
ājñāpayati no yatra rājā svāmī prajeśvaraḥ|| 102.15||
tadvayaṃ śirasā sarve kariṣyāma na saṃśayaḥ|
yadaśaktā vayaṃ kāryaṃ sarve 'apyasurapuṃgavaḥ|
kartuṃ tasya bhavān kartā mā naḥ paśya parāniva|| 102.16||
mṛgārthe danudaityānāṃ svayaṃ rājā mahābalaḥ|
nirgato nāsti daityānāṃ vakṣyanti balam ityuta|| 102.17||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa rājā daityānāṃ sarvāneva samādiśat|
kāle jaladharānindro yathā bhinnāñjanatviṣaḥ|| 102.18||
ājñāṃ tasya gṛhītvaiva te 'api daityā mudānvitāḥ|
saṃnahyanta mahākāyā vāhanāni ca bhejire|| 102.19||
prahlādaścānuhlādaśca śinirbāṣkala eva ca|
jambhaḥ kujambho vātāpī ilvalo 'atha virocanaḥ|| 102.20||
balirbāṇaśca vātaśca śambhuḥ kaśyapa eva ca|
śamabaraśca mahākāyaḥ kālaśambara eva ca|| 102.21||
pradīptaścāsilomā ca śilitāścaiva dānavāḥ|
sarabhaḥ śalabhaścaiva dhundhurmūkaśca dānavaḥ|| 102.22||
śatodaraśca vikhyātastathaivānyo hradodaraḥ|
tāraśca tārakaścaiva mayaḥ kālaśca viśrutaḥ|| 102.23||
ajako namuciścaiva vyaṃsaḥ kārtasvanaḥ śubhaḥ|
ilvako bilvakaścaiva vipākaḥ pāka eva ca|| 102.24||
hasto duryodhanaścaiva vipracittiśca dānavaḥ|
hayagrīvo muraścaiva narakaḥ kuṇḍa eva ca|| 102.25||
śakunirvṛṣaparvā ca śataketurmahāravaḥ|
marakaścaiva rāhuśca svarbhānuḥ kāla eva ca|| 102.26||
virādhaśca kabandhaśca dundubhiḥ śatadundubhiḥ|
śālvo drumaśca dvāvetau mayūragrīva eva ca|| 102.27||
kālanemī meghanādo mahāvīryaḥ sa cāndhakaḥ|
mahiṣānandaśamakāvāṭiśca baka eva ca|| 102.28||
tato dānavaśārdūlā mahāmāyā mahābalāḥ|
sarve sarvāstraviduṣo labdhalakṣāśca saṃyuge|| 102.29||
rathairhayairgajaiśca tathaivānye padātayaḥ|
jagmurvarāhaṃ taṃ vyāsa hantuṃ devā ivāsuram|| 102.30||
sa cāpi hi mahātejā varāho nandivardhanaḥ|
stūyamānastathātmasthairmunibhirbhagavān balī|| 102.31||
hatvā tān kiṃkarān sarvānaśmakaṃ puram āgamat|
garjamāno yathā megho yugānte vṛṣṭisarjanaḥ|| 102.32||
sa gatvā tat tadā vyāsa puraṃ lokamayaḥ prabhuḥ|
apasavyaṃ purāvṛtya dakṣiṇaṃ dvāram āgamat|| 102.33||
dakṣiṇadvāribhistatra dānavairbahubhirbhṛśam|
kṛto halāhalāśabdo nagaraṃ yena kopitam|| 102.34||
yo hi bhittvā śataghnīśca kavāṭaṃ kūṭamudgarān|
kālacakrāṇi yantrāṇi so 'avacūrṇayadavyayaḥ|| 102.35||
athājagmurbhṛśāviṣṭāste dānavamahārathāḥ|
śastravarṣeṇa cogreṇa chādayanto mṛgeśvaram|| 102.36||
atha taistomaraiścakrairbhindīpāpālaiśca tāḍitaḥ|
dvāraṃ tyaktvā vinirgamya samāṃ bhūmim upāśritaḥ|| 102.37||
te 'api taṃ bhagnam ityeva vijānanto 'asurāstadā|
pṛṣṭhato 'anuyayurvyāsa takṣayanto varāyudhaiḥ|| 102.38||
sa takṣyamāṇaḥ śaravṛṣṭitomarairmahāgadābhirmuśalairayomukhaiḥ|
tadābhiniḥsṛtya diteḥ sutānasāvayodhayaddevagaṇairadhiṣṭhitaḥ|| 102.39||
iti skandapurāṇe asurasaṃdeśanaṃ nāma dvyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 102.102||

skandapurana103
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha vyāsa samāṃ bhūmiṃ samprāptān dānavarṣabhān|
uvāca sarvān gambhīraṃ mṛgān siṃha ivājane|| 103.1||
bhavanto dānavāḥ sarve daityāśca sumahābalāḥ|
mayā mṛgeṇa samare yudhyatāṃ tu punarbhṛśam|| 103.2||
na lajjā samare 'abhyetya yuṣmākaṃ dānaveśvarāḥ|
atha vā na balaṃ vo 'asti mithyā devā hi vo jitāḥ|| 103.3||
bahavo balavantaśca mṛgaścāhaṃ vanecaraḥ|
na manye dharmayuddhe vo matirdānavasattamāḥ|| 103.4||
na mamāsti dhanuḥ kiṃcinna śastraṃ ca tathāvidham|
saśastrairbahubhiryena yuddheyam asureśvarāḥ|| 103.5||
te yūyaṃ yadi manyadhvaṃ śastrāṇi tyajatādhunā|
mayā caikaikaśaḥ sarve yudhyadhvaṃ nyāyam āsthitāḥ|| 103.6||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā so 'andhako dānaveśvaraḥ|
uvāca sarvān daityendrān yugāntāmbudavannadan|| 103.7||
evam etadyathāhāyaṃ mṛgo 'asuramahārathāḥ|
saṃtyajāmādya śastrāṇi yodhām ekaikaśastathā|| 103.8||
prahlāda uvāca|
abuddhireṣā daityendrā yathāhāyaṃ mṛgādhamaḥ|
samānānāṃ samaiḥ sārdham etadyuddhaṃ praśasyate|| 103.9||
na mṛgāṇāṃ ca śastrāṇi na bāhubalam ityuta|
vadhyante ca sadā śastraireṣa dharmaḥ stāṃ mataḥ|| 103.10||
te vayaṃ katham utsṛjya svadharmaṃ dānaveśvarāḥ|
mṛgadharmaṃ samāsthāya yudhyema paśavo yathā|| 103.11||
mṛgādhamo 'ayaṃ durvṛtto 'avadhyo nāsmādibhiḥ|
-- -- -- mā vicāro vo mṛge bhavatu sarvaśaḥ|| 103.12||
māyām āsthāya duṣṭātmā ko 'apyayaṃ surapāṃsanaḥ|
asmān vañcayituṃ daityāḥ kāṅkṣate sudurātmavān|| 103.13||
kva ca śrutaṃ vā dṛṣṭaṃ vā mṛgāṇām asureśvarāḥ|
manuṣyavadbāhuyuddhaṃ puruṣaiḥ saha saṃyuge|| 103.14||
eṣa viṣṇurdurācāro durātmā daityakaṇṭakaḥ|
aśaktaḥ svena vīryeṇa māyām āsthāya saṃsthitaḥ|| 103.15||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastaṃ balavān kruddho dhanuṣā so 'asureśvaraḥ|
śarairavākiradvyāsa bahubhirvirarāsa ca|| 103.16||
andhako vipracittiśca sarve te daityadānavāḥ|
avākiran śaraistīkṣṇaiḥ śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|| 103.17||
atha devaḥ susaṃrabdhairviddhaistairdānavairbhṛśam|
śuśubhe bhāskarakaraiḥ saṃviddho himavāniva|| 103.18||
sa vegaṃ balavat kṛtvā vidhunvānaḥ śarān śitān|
salīlaṃ prayayau devaḥ prahlādaṃ prati dānavam|| 103.19||
sa gatvā tasya sahasā sārathiṃ ratham eva ca|
daṃṣṭrābhiśca karābhyāṃ ca nāmaśeṣaṃ cakāra ha|| 103.20||
tato rathādavaplutya hanyamāno 'api dānavaiḥ|
rathadhvajena taṃ daityaṃ mūrdhni devo 'abhijaghnivān|| 103.21||
prahlādo 'api tatotpatya gadayā bhīmarūpayā|
ājaghānorasi kruddhaṃ vighno dharme yathā sthitam|| 103.22||
sa tenābhihato devo muktvā tasya rathaṃ tadā|
tam eva deśam āyātaḥ pūrvaṃ yatrābhavat sthitaḥ|| 103.23||
tato 'andhako vipracittiḥ śambaraḥ kālaśambaraḥ|
śarairāśīviṣākārairbibhidurindravardhanam|| 103.24||
sa viddhastaistadā vyāsa śaraiḥ saṃnataparvabhiḥ|
bhidyamānaśca bahudhā maṇḍalāni cacāra ha|| 103.25||
kadācit siṃhavaccāpi plavate nardate 'api ca|
śārdūlavat kadācicca bhumau ātmānam āhave|| 103.26||
vitatya sa mahāvīryastiṣṭhate sāyakān sahan|
pādena tata utthāya avakīrya vṛṣo yathā|| 103.27||
pakṣivat sa tadākāśe maṇḍalāni mṛgeśvaraḥ|
bhramitvā niścalastasthau varāhaḥ parvato yathā|| 103.28||
evaṃ bahuvidhān mārgān vicaritvā mahābalaḥ|
vegenaiva karābhyāṃ sa rathau jagrāha nādayan|| 103.29||
vipracitteśca balavānandhakasya ca suprabhaḥ|
bhrāmayitvā muhūrtaṃ tau sahāśvaiḥ sahasārathī|| 103.30||
bhūmāvutkṣipya cikṣepa babhañja ca punaḥ padā|
rathāsthitau ca tau daityau punarmūrdhanyatāḍayat|| 103.31||
tau hatāvatisaṃkruddhau gade codyamya vegitau|
varāhaṃ mūrdhni yugapat samāhatya vinedatuḥ|| 103.32||
tābhyāṃ sa balavān kruddho hastābhyāṃ raktalocanaḥ|
gade jagrāha yat tābhyāṃ balādeva mṛgeśvaraḥ|| 103.33||
tato 'acaranmaṇḍalāni vividhāni janārdanaḥ|
gadāviśāradaḥ samyagvicitrāṇi bahūnyapi|| 103.34||
ākṣiptam atha vikṣiptam avākṣiptaṃ ca maṇḍalam|
utkṣiptam atha vikṣiptaṃ visṛṣṭaṃ dhāvitaṃ tathā|| 103.35||
parāvṛttaṃ nivṛttaṃ ca ardhacandram athāpi ca|
viṣṭabdhaṃ codyataṃ caiva haṃsodbhramitam eva ca|| 103.36||
gadāviśāradaḥ samyagbhramitvā maṇḍalāni saḥ|
gadām upari cikṣepa so 'andhakasya vinādayan|| 103.37||
aparāṃ vipracitteśca balavān nandivardhanaḥ|
te gade tau mahāvege dānavau sudurāsadau|| 103.38||
vañcayitvā raṇe bhūyo varāhaṃ prati dānavau|
ādhāvitau yathā deśam utpātau vegitāveva|| 103.39||
tayorāpatatoreva varāho 'asau mahābalaḥ|
muṣṭināndhakam āhatya vipracittiṃ padāvadhīt|| 103.40||
andhakastasya muṣṭiṃ taṃ vipracittiḥ padaṃ ca ha|
kruddhau jagṛhaturdaityau hatastvam iti vādinau|| 103.41||
nādayānau yathā kāle kṛṣṇāviva balāhakau|
sa gṛhītastadā tābhyāṃ mahātmā surasattamaḥ|| 103.42||
utpapāta viyadvegāt pakṣirāḍiva kāśyapaḥ|
viyatstho vibabhau daityāvudvahan sa mṛgeśvaraḥ|| 103.43||
garutmāniva pakṣīśo bhakṣārthaṃ gajakaccahapau|
vinadya sa tadākāśe vidhūya ca karau balī|| 103.44||
pādaṃ caivābhicikṣepa tau daityau bhujagāviva|
tau kṣiptau prekṣya tu vyāsa dānavau yuddhadurmadau|| 103.45||
abhiyātau mahīṃ ghorāvaśanī khāccyutāviva|
asāvapi ca deveśo varāho nandivardhanaḥ|
rathān vai sarvadaityānāṃ cūrṇayāmāsa vīryavān|| 103.46||
gṛhītvā kūbare kaṃcit soccikṣepa mahārṇave|
kaṃcit padā samāhatya pāṃsusāyujyam ānayat|| 103.47||
kaṃcidrathaṃ rathenaiva padātiṃ ca padātinā|
gajaṃ gajena cāhatya sa ninye yamasādanam|| 103.48||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te 'api vidrāvitāḥ sarva lajjāṃ paramikāṃ gatāḥ|
daityadānavaśārdūlā vinivṛttā yathābalāḥ|| 103.49||
ekena sarve vijitāsurendrāḥ parasparaṃ vīkṣya mukhāni śūrāḥ|
vrīḍānvitāste punareva devaṃ varāha ---- -- -- -- -- -- ti|| 103.50||
iti skandapurāṇe varāhayuddhe tryuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 103.103||

skandapurana104
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha te taṃ mṛgaṃ vyāsa dānavā bhīmagarjanāḥ|
āyudhaiḥ samabhikruddhāḥ saṃtatakṣustadā bhṛśam|| 104.1||
te mṛgā iva śārdūlaṃ siṃhapotaṃ gajā iva|
ājaghnurdānavāḥ kruddhā varāhaṃ śastravṛṣṭibhiḥ|| 104.2||
sa cāpi mṛgaśārdūla upaviśya mahodadhim|
apo 'apibat samāviśya vahnivadvaḍavāmukham|| 104.3||
tatheritāni tairdaityairāyudhāni sahasraśaḥ|
vyādāya sumahadvaktraṃ jagrāsa ca rarāsa ca|| 104.4||
grasitvā tāni sarvāṇi śastrāṇi sa mahābalaḥ|
dānavān prati saṃcakre vegaṃ sindhurivāparaḥ|| 104.5||
gajān prati yathā siṃhaḥ siṃhān śarabharāḍiva|
garutmān bhujagān yadvacchārdūlaśca mṛgāniva|| 104.6||
meghavṛndaṃ yathā vāyuḥ kapotāniva pakṣirāṭ|
tathā sa bhagavān vyāsa dānavān prati lokapaḥ|| 104.7||
vegaṃ cakre yathā kṣipram indriyaṃ prati vai manaḥ|
āsādya ca sa tān daityān mahājaladaniḥsvanaḥ|| 104.8||
sarvān vidrāvayāmāsa rudraḥ paśugaṇāniva|
kāṃścit padbhyāṃ susaṃkruddho hastābhyām aparāniti|| 104.9||
daṃṣṭrābhiścāparāṃstatra sa praiṣīdyamasādanam|
tuṇḍena śambaraṃ bhūmau kālaśambaram eva ca|| 104.10||
narakaṃ pādaghātena hayagrīvaṃ ca muṣṭinā|
urasā namuciṃ cāpi mahāmāyaṃ ca satvaraḥ|| 104.11||
āhatyāhatya saṃkruddhaḥ pātayāmāsa devapaḥ|
tāṃstathā drāvayānaṃ ca garjamānaṃ ca siṃhavat|| 104.12||
vipracittirvarāhaṃ taṃ muṣṭinorasyatāḍayat|
vipracittiṃ jaghānograṃ pārśvadeśe sa muṣṭinā|| 104.13||
sa āhato varāheṇa varāhaṃ krodhamūrchitaḥ|
punarjaghāna khaḍgena vakṣasyenaṃ vinādayan|| 104.14||
amṛṣyamāṇastaṃ ghātaṃ varāhaḥ sumahābalaḥ|
muṣṭinā mūrdhni taṃ daityaṃ vajrābhena vyatāḍayat|| 104.15||
sa daityastena ghātena bhramitvā cakravat tadā|
papāta bhūmau vegena vātāhata iva drumaḥ|| 104.16||
patitaṃ taṃ tadābhyetya vipracittiṃ prajeśvaraḥ|
jagrāha padbhyāṃ deveśo drāvamāṇaṃ diteḥ sutam|| 104.17||
bhrāmayitvā tataścainaṃ narditvā cāsakṛdbalī|
puraṃ prati vicikṣepa mahātmā nandivardhanaḥ|| 104.18||
sa kṣiptastena vibabhau dānavādhipatirbalī|
sabalākataḍijjvālaparicchinna ivāmbudaḥ|| 104.19||
srastahārāmbaradharaścyutamālyavibhūṣaṇaḥ|
papātopari vegena hiraṇyākṣasya veśmani|| 104.20||
saudham aṭṭālakaṃ tasya vimānam iva saṃsthitam|
cūrṇayāno 'apatadvyāsa parvatendram ivāśaniḥ|| 104.21||
mahatā tasya śabdena hiraṇyākṣaḥ svayaṃ tadā|
vegenāgatya dadṛśe dānavendraṃ diteḥ sutaḥ|| 104.22||
so 'api dānavaśārdūlo varāheṇāvapīḍitaḥ|
tena caiva vighātena muhūrtam abhavajjaḍaḥ|| 104.23||
taṃ samāśvāsayadrājā tadā śītena vāriṇā|
tālavṛntaiśca bahubhirmaṇibhiśca diteḥ sutaḥ|| 104.24||
samāśvasyotthitaṃ caiva upaviṣṭaṃ varāsane|
rājā papraccha taṃ daityaṃ paraṃ vismayam āgataḥ|| 104.25||
hiraṇyākṣa uvāca|
kenādya himavān daitya pṛthivī vā sasāgarā|
mahābalena sahasā tulitā viśvakarmaṇā|| 104.26||
kenādya mandaraḥ srasto mṛtyuḥ kena parājitaḥ|
kena tvaṃ dānaveśāna kṣiptaḥ ko balavān bhuvi|| 104.27||
pṛthivyāstulanaṃ yādṛṅmandarasya ca cālanam|
mṛtyośca maraṇaṃ tādṛk tavedaṃ kṣepaṇaṃ mahat|| 104.28||
rudrendramṛtyupratimo lokapālabhayaṃkaraḥ|
kena tvaṃ tulitaḥ saṃkhye balavānabalo yathā|| 104.29||
kasyedaṃ balam akṣayyaṃ kena bāhvorbalaṃ mahat|
khāpitaṃ triṣu lokeṣu dānaveśvara kathyatām|| 104.30||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā dānavaḥ sa mahābalaḥ|
tam āha dīrghaṃ niḥśvasya nirīkṣya ca punaḥ punaḥ|| 104.31||
vipracittiruvāca|
amānuṣam idaṃ rājannatidevaṃ tathāpi ca|
atidaityaṃ ca daityendra na dṛṣṭaṃ na śrutaṃ kvacit|| 104.32||
varāhasya balaṃ yādṛṅna ca tādṛk kvacit kvacit|
na hi tulyaṃ prapaśyāmi tasya rājan mahātmanaḥ|| 104.33||
astraiḥ śastraiśca bahubhistakṣyamāṇasya saṃyuge|
nārtirna duḥkhaṃ daityendra na ca saṃjñā prahīyate|| 104.34||
bhavet tasyābhidaṣṭasya maśakenāpyanirvṛtiḥ|
na daityadānavai rājan nighnasya bhayam ityuta|| 104.35||
yathā kṣudramṛgān siṃho maṇḍūkāniva voragaḥ|
tathā sa kalayāmāsa sarvān daityendradānavān|| 104.36||
na taṃ mṛgam ahaṃ manye na devaṃ nāpi cāsuram|
ko 'apyasau ditiputrāṇām anayaḥ samupasthitaḥ|| 104.37||
tenāsmi muṣṭinā mūrdhni tāḍito bhūtalaṃ gataḥ|
gṛhītvā sahasotkṣiptaḥ patitastvadgṛhupari|| 104.38||
dānavānāṃ sadaityānām itareṣāṃ ca dānava|
na jāne samavasthānaṃ manye te sarvaśo hatāḥ|| 104.39||
avadhyaḥ sa mahātejā balavān durbalā vayam|
śrutvaitadditiputrāṇāṃ hitaṃ yat tat samācara|| 104.40||
tasyāṅge munayaḥ sarve dṛśyante saha daivataiḥ|
kṛtyā seti mataṃ me 'adya tava hetorvinirmitā|| 104.41||
manaśca tava daityendra yuddhāya kṛtaniścayam|
vinivartaya taccaiva daityānāṃ hitam ācara|| 104.42||
balavān so 'abalā daityā vayaṃ martyāḥ sa cāmaraḥ|
ajayyo 'asau jitā daityā mā no yuddhena yojaya|| 104.43||
hitvāśmakaṃ puraṃ sarve samudrastambham āśritāḥ|
tiṣṭhāma rājan mā yuddhaṃ tena sākaṃ punaḥ kṛthāḥ|| 104.44||
māvaṃsthā mṛgaṃ daitya mṛgo 'asāviti sarvaśaḥ|
narasiṃho 'apyabhūt pūrvaṃ mṛgastadvinibṛṃhitaḥ|| 104.45||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
yāvat tvaṃ dhriyase daitya dānavānāṃ sukhāvahaḥ|
tāvat sarve 'asurā jīvā bhaviṣyanti na saṃśayaḥ|| 104.46||
mā ruśantu diteḥ putrā danoścaiva subāliśāḥ|
apayāma purādasmādasureśvara sarvaśaḥ|| 104.47||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca dānaveśānaṃ bhītaṃ tasmānmahātmanaḥ|| 104.48||
asaṃśayaṃ mahātmāsau mṛgo dānavasattama|
yena mandarakalpastvaṃ tulitaḥ sumahābalaḥ|| 104.49||
adya varṣasahasrāṇi divyānyasurapuṃgava|
catvāri bhuñjato rājyaṃ gatāni sumahānti me|| 104.50||
pañcapañcā tu samprāptaṃstāvaddevāśca nāśitāḥ|
sabalā bahubhirghoraiḥ saṃgrāmairabalā iva|| 104.51||
so 'ahaṃ tathā balopeto bhuktvā rājyam akaṇṭakam|
bhītaḥ praviśya salilaṃ kathaṃ sthāsye bhujaṃgavat|| 104.52||
mṛgarūpī sa viṣṇuśca vārāhaṃ rūpam āsthitaḥ|
yadi syāt tacca kṛtyaṃ me dānaveśvara mā bhayam|| 104.53||
mamāpi balam akṣayyaṃ tasmācca balavānaham|
yo me bhayāt parityajya svaṃ rūpaṃ mṛgatāṃ gataḥ|| 104.54||
yo hanyāddhastinaṃ saṃkhye siṃhaṃ śarabham eva ca|
tasya kāsthā bhaveddaitya mṛge hyasmin mahābala|| 104.55||
madbhayāt sa varāhaśca sarvadevairadhiṣṭhitaḥ|
mām āhvayati daityendra jaya eva tato hi me|| 104.56||
bhavāneva hi me daitya tena dūtaḥ -- -- -- --|
tvaratā mṛtyulokaṃ tu gatvā dānavapuṃgava|| 104.57||
yadahaṃ mrātṛhantāraṃ dānavānāṃ bhayaṃkaram|
ahatvā na nivartiṣye śape satyena dānava|| 104.58||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sūtaṃ tataḥ samāviśya rathaṃ sajjam acīkarat|
samāśvāsayituṃ patnīḥ sa viveśa punargṛhān|| 104.59||
sa tatra tābhiḥ kṛtamaṅgalastadā diteḥ sutāṃstāṃśca nirīkṣya sarvaśaḥ|
gṛhāṇa sarvaṃ raṇayogyam ujjvalaṃ mahābalaḥ śatrunivāraṇakṣamam|| 104.60||
iti skandapurāṇe vipracittipātane caturuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 104.104||

skandapurana105
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa dhanvī kavacī bhūtvā baddhagodhāṅgulitravān|
baddhapṛṣṭheṣudhī caiva śarī khaḍgī mahābalaḥ|| 105.1||
hariśmaśruścaturdaṃṣṭraḥ śaṅkukarṇo mahāhanuḥ|
ājānubāhurdīrghākṣo nyagrodhaparimaṇḍalaḥ|| 105.2||
hastayoḥ padmaśaṅkhau ca cakramatsyau ca pādayoḥ|
dadhāno jālahastaśca jālapādo 'alpamehanaḥ|| 105.3||
bālādityanibhākṣaśca añjanācalasaṃnibhaḥ|
sa niryayau tadā vyāsa bhṛkuṭībhūṣitānanaḥ|| 105.4||
dvāryapaśyacca sūtena rathaṃ samupakalpitam|
sahasranalvamātraṃ ca hayairdivyaiḥ samanvitam|| 105.5||
sahasrairdaśabhirvyāsa sarvopakaraṇānvitam|
khaṭvāṅgena ca saṃyuktaṃ dhvajenādityavarcasā|| 105.6||
āruroha jayetyukto dānavairbahubhistadā|
divākaro rahtaṃ yadvadbhagavāṃstejasāṃ patiḥ|| 105.7||
vibabhau sa tadārūḍho rathaṃ taṃ ditinandanaḥ|
sauvarṇo bhājane yadvadindranīlaṃ samarpitam|| 105.8||
kirīṭastu ābabhau tasya śirasthaḥ sumahādyutiḥ|
yathāñjanagireḥ śṛṅge dāvāgniḥ samavasthitaḥ|| 105.9||
saṃcodayacca yantāraṃ sa daityo gamanaṃ prati|
tasya pārśve 'abhavadvyāsa vipracittiravasthitaḥ|| 105.10||
ketoriva yathā vyomni pratiketuravasthitaḥ|
śaṅkhabherīmṛdaṅgaiśca murajairveṇubhistathā|| 105.11||
vādyamānairyayau rājā hiraṇyākṣo 'aśmakāt purāt|
agrataḥ pṛṣṭhataścaiva pārśvayorubhayorapi|| 105.12||
jagmuḥ sarve 'asurā vyāsa bhāskarasya yathā grahāḥ|
nirgacchamānaśca purāt śakuntān bhayaśaṃsinaḥ|| 105.13||
apaśyadvyāsa daityendro na ca tānakaroddhṛdi|
āchinat tasya panthānaṃ bhujaṃgaḥ kṛṣṇadehavān|| 105.14||
gṛdhraśca raktavaktro 'asya nililye dhvajamūrdhani|
gṛdhraścakrāyate cāsya rathasyopari gacchataḥ|| 105.15||
dhvajaścābhajyata mahān rathasya sumahāprabhaḥ|
vāmaṃ cāṅgaṃ sphuratyasya śarīrasya muhurmuhuḥ|| 105.16||
heṣante na hayā dīnā hastino vimadābhavan|
etānyanyāni ca bahūni daityo munisattama|| 105.17||
so 'avaikṣata nimittāni bhayadāni ātmano 'asakṛt|
nātidūre sa nirgatya nagarasya mṛgeśvaram|| 105.18||
apaśyaddānavaḥ saṃkhye yudhyamānam abhītavat|
so 'api daityavaraḥ śrīmān krodhasaṃraktalocanaḥ|| 105.19||
visphārayanmahācāpaṃ rathenābhyapatadbalī|
varāho 'api mahābāhurvidrāvya ditinandanān|
suvarṇākṣaṃ prati ruṣā vegenaivābhyadhāvata|| 105.20||
tasyāpatata evāśu dānavaḥ sumahābalaḥ|
sarvasandhiṣu tīkṣṇāgrān nicakhāna bahūñcharān|| 105.21||
sāyakaistairvinirbhinnaḥ sarvasandhiṣu suvrata|
na cacāla mṛgendro 'asau viṣṭabdhaḥ samatiṣṭhata|| 105.22||
taṃ stambhitaṃ tadā vyāsa dṛṣṭvā devā mahābalam|
viśalyakaraṇairmantrairviśalyam abhicakrire|| 105.23||
sa viśalyastadā devaiḥ kṛto mṛgapatirmahān|
punarvegaṃ mahat kṛtvā jagāma ditijaṃ prati|| 105.24||
sa vadhyamāno bahubhiḥ śarairmṛgapatirmahān|
daityendraratham āsādya iyeṣa ratham avyayaḥ|| 105.25||
grahītuṃ nādayan vyāsa bahudhā viśvarūpadhṛk|
yantā ca maṇḍalaṃ kṛtvā bhrāmayāmāsa taṃ ratham|| 105.26||
prasāritakaraṃ daityo mṛgaṃ taṃ sumahābalam|
babandhāstreṇa nāgānāṃ sa baddho nyapatadbhuvi|| 105.27||
patitaṃ taṃ ca daityendro vividhāyudhapāṇayaḥ|
vijaghnurbhṛśam āyastā bahudhā krodhamūrchitāḥ|| 105.28||
taṃ baddhaṃ vadhyamānaṃ ca patitaṃ nandivardhanam|
garutmān bhujagendrebhyaḥ kṣipram eva vyamocayat|| 105.29||
muktaśca sa tadotpatya drāvayāṇo diteḥ sutān|
hiraṇyākṣarathaṃ tūrṇam abhyadhāvan mahāyaśāḥ|| 105.30||
taṃ dhāvantaṃ punardaityaḥ śareṇānataparvaṇā|
vivyādha hṛdaye vyāsa nardamāno yathāmbudaḥ|| 105.31||
mṛgeśvaraśca bhinno 'asau hṛdaye moham āsthitaḥ|
papāta bhūmau nirvṛtte śakradhvaja ivotsave|| 105.32||
tato hā hā kṛtaṃ sarvaiḥ sametairdevapuṃgavaiḥ|
ṛṣayastuṣṭuvuścainaṃ bhāskaraścāprabho 'abhavat|| 105.33||
atha sopyāyitastatra ṛṣibhirbrahmavittamaiḥ|
pratilabhya tadā saṃjñām idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 105.34||
āpyāyayadhvaṃ māṃ kṣipraṃ mūḍho 'ahaṃ sarvaśaḥ surāḥ|
nālpavīryeṇa śakyo 'ayaṃ daityo yodhayituṃ raṇe|| 105.35||
tataste daivatāḥ sarve ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
tapasā svena taṃ devaṃ sarva evābhyapūrayan|| 105.36||
tasya tu āpyāyamānasya ṛṣibhirdaivataiśca ha|
babhau rūpaṃ yugāntāgnikālamṛtyusamaprabham|| 105.37||
sa dīpamāno vibabhau mahātmā devaiśca sarvairṛṣibhiḥ stutaśca|
dīptastadā bhāskarasaptakalpo lokān dahiṣyanniva devadevaḥ|| 105.38||
iti skandapurāṇe varāhāpyāyane pañcottaraśato .adhyāyaḥ|| 105.105||

skandapurana106
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa tathāpyāyito vyāsa balavān bhāskaradyutiḥ|
citraṃ bahu ca śīghraṃ ca maṇḍalāni paribhramat|| 106.1||
plutāni siṃhavat kṛtvā avalokayate 'asakṛt|
pṛṣṭhataścāgrataścāpi punargajavadācarat|| 106.2||
punarvyāttānano bhūtvā śatrāṇi grasate ripoḥ|
punarvṛkṣaiḥ śilābhiśca dānavān sa nyasūdayat|| 106.3||
punarākāśago bhūtvā pakṣirāḍiva so 'abhramat|
punarjahāsa saṃkruddho hyaśanīpātasaṃnibham|| 106.4||
punaśca sūkṣmam ātmānaṃ kṛtvā tasthāvathāgrataḥ|
evaṃ taṃ valgamānaṃ ca nardamānaṃ ca dānavaḥ|| 106.5||
uvāca bhṛkuṭīvaktro hiraṇyākṣo 'abhinādayan|
bho kṣudramṛga durbuddhe na tvaṃ mokṣam avāpsyasi|| 106.6||
hatvā tvāhaṃ pradāsyāmi rudrāya balim ojasā|
tvayā hataśchadmanā me bhrātā jyeṣṭho durātmanā|
tasyādya karmaṇaḥ prāptaṃ phalaṃ duṣṭātmanastava|| 106.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā hiraṇyākṣasya saṃyuge|
uvāca bhagavān viṣṇuḥ krodhayāno diteḥ sutam|| 106.8||
hato 'asau narasiṃhena mayā daityaḥ pratāpavān|
vikramya saṃyuge tadvadbhavato 'api vadho dhruvaḥ|| 106.9||
yadi tvaṃ gacchase khaṃ vā pātālaṃ vāpyataḥ param|
parvataṃ vodadhiṃ vāpi na tathāpi vimokṣyase|| 106.10||
yat te balaṃ tapo yacca yā ca māyā tavāsura|
tat sarvaṃ nirdhamāmyadya tava dehāt sajīvitam|| 106.11||
hiraṇyākṣa uvāca|
tvaṃ mayā śaraviṣṭabdho devairmantrairvimokṣitaḥ|
baddhaṃ cāstreṇa bhūyastvāṃ pakṣirājo vyamocayat|| 106.12||
bhūyo mṛtastvaṃ durbuddhe devairujjīvito bhavaḥ|
bhūyastvāhaṃ vadhiṣyāmi siṃho mṛgam ivājane|| 106.13||
tava kā śaktiradyeha maheśvaram ṛte varam|
māṃ spraṣṭum api hastena narasyeva hutāśanam|| 106.14||
tvaṃ lokamayam āsthāya śarīraṃ tairadhiṣṭhitam|
sarvairāpyāyitaścaiva saṃyuge mām upāgataḥ|| 106.15||
ahaṃ tu svena tapasā balena ca samanvitaḥ|
na ca māṃ tvaṃ tathāpyadya śaktaḥ siṃhaṃ yathā mṛgaḥ|| 106.16||
yoddhuṃ vāpyabhisartuṃ vā saha devairdurātmavān|
na tu āvayoretadeva hyantaraṃ sumahattaram|| 106.17||
yaḥ syāt kulīno vidvān vā satāṃ mārge ca saṃsthitaḥ|
so 'anenaiva jitaṃ matvā ātmānaṃ saṃyugaṃ tyajet|| 106.18||
nirghṛnastyaktalajjaśca chidraghātī durātmavān|
tvadanyaḥ ko bhavet tiryaṅnaitaddaityasya vidyate|| 106.19||
na tvaṃ mama kṛto mṛtyurahaṃ tu tava saṃyuge|
ete siddhāḥ prapaśyantu cāraṇāśca sahasraśaḥ|
āvayorantaraṃ saṃkhye bahudhā yudhyamānayoḥ|| 106.20||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā hiraṇyākṣaḥ śarairāśīviṣopamaiḥ|
jaghne varāhaṃ saṃkruddho vajrāśanisamatviṣam|| 106.21||
so 'atha tenārdyamāno 'api varāhaḥ sumahābalaḥ|
gatvā vegena saṃkruddho rathaṃ jagrāha nādayan|| 106.22||
gṛhītvā kūbare cāpi ākṣipyotkṣipya vegavat|
sāśvaṃ sasārathiṃ devaścikṣepa ca rarāsa ca|| 106.23||
tasya tu ākṣepavikṣepaiśchinnayoktrāśca te hayāḥ|
udbhrāntā rathamukhyaśca visandhiḥ samapadyata|| 106.24||
hiraṇyākṣo rathaṃ tyaktvā padātirdhanuṣā tadā|
mṛgendraṃ mohanāstreṇa balavānabhyatāḍayat|| 106.25||
mohaḥ samāviśaccaiva taṃ devaṃ nandivardhanam|
devairmantraprabhāveṇa naṣṭamohaḥ kṛtaḥ punaḥ|| 106.26||
eṣa śastrairbahuvidhairdaityendro hi ruṣānvitaḥ|
ājaghāna na cāpyenaṃ rujā sa samayojayat|| 106.27||
athainaṃ sa mahātejā varāhaḥ prahasanniva|
vṛkṣam utpāṭya vegena daityaṃ mūrdhni vyatāḍayat|| 106.28||
tasya tena prahāreṇa daityasyābhihatasya ha|
dhanuḥ papāta vegena hastāvāpaśca pañcakaḥ|| 106.29||
tato hā hā kṛtaṃ daityairdānavaiśca suduḥkhitaiḥ|
śastraiśca bahubhiḥ kruddhā varāhaṃ samatāḍayan|| 106.30||
sa hanyamānastairdaityairvyadāya sumahābalaḥ|
mukhaṃ sarvāṇi śastrāṇi jagrāsa ca rarāsa ca|| 106.31||
tat tathā vikṛtaṃ dṛṣṭvā hiraṇyākṣaḥ pratāpavān|
śūlaṃ jagrāha saṃkruddhaḥ kṛtvā rudrāya vai namaḥ|| 106.32||
tadyugāntānalaprakhyaṃ mahāśūlam atiprabham|
cikṣepa daityaḥ saṃkruddho varāhāya mahāsvanam|| 106.33||
tam āpatantaṃ bahudhā nadantaṃ jvālāḥ sphuliṅgāśca samudgirantam|
dṛṣṭvā surāḥ siddhagaṇāśca sarve hā heti cakrurbhayamūḍhacittāḥ|| 106.34||
iti skandapurāṇe triśūlākṣepaṇe ṣaḍuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 106.106||

skandapurana107
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tam āpatantaṃ vegena na śūlaṃ dṛṣṭavān mṛgaḥ|
daityasandhe samāsaktaḥ sarvaprāṇibhayaṃkaram|| 107.1||
alakṣitena tenāsau śūlenāditinandanaḥ|
vibhinno hṛdaye vyāsa mṛtakalpaḥ papāta ha|| 107.2||
tato hā hā kṛtaṃ bhūtairadṛśyairmunisattama|
udvelāḥ sāgarāścāsan bhāskaraścāprabho 'abhavat|| 107.3||
ulkāḥ petuśca sarvatra mlānamālyāḥ surābhavan|
grahāṇām abhavadyuddhaṃ vimānāni ca petire|| 107.4||
jajapurmunayaḥ sarve varāhe patite tadā|
mahādevaṃ namaskṛtya brahmā saṃsmāra taṃ tadā|| 107.5||
tato vitimiraṃ sarvam abhavat pūrvavacchubham|
mahādevaṃ namaskṛtya varāhaścodatiṣṭhata|| 107.6||
tejo māheśvaraṃ divyaṃ viveśa madhusūdanam|
sopyāyitatanustena śūlaṃ niṣkṛṣya mādhavaḥ|| 107.7||
sahasānalasaṃkāśo babhūva sa mahābalaḥ|
tatastenaiva śūlena taṃ daityaṃ devanandanaḥ|| 107.8||
jaghāna hṛdaye kruddhaḥ krauñcaṃ śaktyā yathā guhaḥ|
sa bhinnahṛdayastena varāheṇa mahāsuraḥ|| 107.9||
nārtimānabhavadvyāsa kṛcchre vidvāniva sthitaḥ|
madhye bhinnaṃ sa tacchūlaṃ niṣkṛṣya ca visṛjya ca|| 107.10||
khaḍgaṃ niṣkṛṣya vegena varāhaṃ mūrdhnyatāḍayat|
sa tena suprahāreṇa varāho nandivardhanaḥ|| 107.11||
nārtimānabhavadvyāsa babhuva rudhirāplutaḥ|
nānādhātuvicitro 'asau himavānava parvataḥ|| 107.12||
babhau varāho devātmā sarvāsuravimardanaḥ|
punarāhantukāmasya tasya daityasya suvrata|| 107.13||
apahastaprahāreṇa khaḍgaṃ hastādapātayat|
akurvātāṃ tato yuddhaṃ niyuddhakuśalāvubhau|| 107.14||
tau gajāviva ca saṃkruddhau mahiṣāviva darpitau|
siṃhāviva ca nardantau saṃkruddhau vṛṣabhāviva|| 107.15||
śarabhāviva cāyastau śārdūlāviva nirghṛṇau|
parasparam ayudhyetāṃ parasparajayaiṣiṇau|| 107.16||
aṅkuśairhastayoktraiśca kṣepaṇairapasarpaṇaiḥ|
maṇlaiśca punaścitraiḥ karṣaṇairapakarṣaṇaiḥ|| 107.17||
talaiśca muṣṭibhiścaiva bhujaiḥ sa caraṇairapi|
nakhaiśca daśanaiścaiva tathānyaiśca mahābalau|| 107.18||
tayos_evam abhūdyuddham ubhayordevadaityayoḥ|
ahāni daśa cāṣṭau ca tathānyāni caturdaśa|| 107.19||
anyat sahasram evāsīdvarṣāṇāṃ tacca mānuṣam|
eṣa kālo 'abhavat tatra tato daityo 'abalo 'abhavat|| 107.20||
taṃ hīyamānam ālakṣya daityādhipatim ūrjitam|
ākāśe vāguvācedam aśarīrātisusvanā|| 107.21||
śṛṇu deva varāhedaṃ śrutvā caiva samācara|
aśakyo 'ayaṃ tvayā hyevaṃ hantuṃ daityo mahābalaḥ|| 107.22||
abalo 'ayaṃ kṛtaḥ krūro dhruvaṃ māheśvareṇa hi|
tejasā paśya caivainam eṣa kālo 'asya vartate|| 107.23||
muktvainaṃ daityarājānaṃ cakr.ena vinisūdaya|
māheśvareṇa vaikuṇṭha tato mṛtyum avāpsyati|| 107.24||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastam abhisaṃśrutya bhagavān nandivardhanaḥ|
mumoca daityarājānaṃ pādenāhatya vakṣasi|| 107.25||
sa muktastena devena vibabhau daityapuṃgavaḥ|
bhuktamukto yathā sūryaḥ saiṃhikeyena rāhuṇā|| 107.26||
bhagavānapi dīpyantaṃ śriyā daityaṃ samīkṣya tam|
sasmāra tat tadā cakraṃ namaskṛtya pinākinam|| 107.27||
tataḥ sarvā diśo vyāsa vahnikuṇḍānibhā babhuḥ|
śabdaśca mumahān āsīdyugāntāmbudasaṃnibhaḥ|| 107.28||
siddhāḥ petuśca medinyāṃ devāṃśca bhayam āviśat|
svastyastu sarvabhūtānām iti ūcurmunayastadā|| 107.29||
sāgarā vyaśuṣyanta vineśurnāgapakṣiṇaḥ|
daityāśca dānavāścaiva sarve te viviśurbilam|| 107.30||
bhayatrastāni bhūtāni ulkāḥ peturnabhastalāt|
āgacchati yugāntāgnikalpe cakre subhāsvare|| 107.31||
kṣurāntaṃ tanmahācakraṃ majjajjalacarāntakam|
durnirīkṣyaṃ sarvadhāti abhedyaṃ pratighāti ca|| 107.32||
tathāpratihataṃ divyaṃ mohanaṃ sarvadehinām|
karam āgādvarāhasya śātāśanisamasvanam|| 107.33||
tadāpatantaṃ saṃvīkṣya sarvabhūtāni sarvataḥ|
peturbhūmau mahāghoram apaśyan na ca kiṃcana|| 107.34||
so 'api devastadā kṛtvā rūpaṃ sumahadavyayam|
trailokyavyāpi cikṣepa dānavaṃ prati nādayan|| 107.35||
tadyugāntānalaprakhyaṃ kṣurāntaṃ sphoṭayan nabhaḥ|
jagāma dānavaṃ kṣipraṃ diśaḥ sarvā dahanniva|| 107.36||
tat sa dānavaśārdūla upayāntaṃ mahāravam|
jaghānāstrairbahuvidhairavyathaḥ śaktinandanaḥ|| 107.37||
tacca tāni mahācakram astrāṇyanalasaṃnibham|
cakāra bhasmasādvyāsa jagāma ca vinādayan|| 107.38||
atha māyāṃ samasṛjat taijasīṃ pārthivīm api|
vāyavīṃ vāruṇīṃ caiva tāmasīm indriyātmikām|| 107.39||
tathaivotpātakīṃ māyāṃ mohanīṃ stambhanīm api|
nivartanīṃ jambhanīṃ ca cakārānyāśca saṃyuge|| 40
tāḥ sarvāstat tadā cakraṃ nāśayadbhīmanādavat|
gatvā tasya śiraḥ kāyādunmamātha yathācalam|| 107.41||
tat tena kṛttaṃ sumahacchiro 'agryaṃ vyāttānanāgnipratimo 'agranetram|
daṃṣṭrālam atyudbhutabhīmanādaṃ papāta meroriva śṛṅgam uccam|| 107.42||
rathāṅguniṣpītavapurvirāgaṃ na bhāti tadvaktram atīva dīnam|
niśāprahāṇe vinivṛttaraśmi bimbaṃ yathā candramaso viśobham|| 107.43||
taddantapaṅkticchadamādaśānaṃ muhuśca dantānapi saṃdaśānam|
papāta daityasya śiro nikṛttaṃ yathā gireḥ śṛṅgam atipravṛddham|| 107.44||
iti skandapurāṇe hiraṇyākṣavadhe saptottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 107.107||

skandapurana108
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasmin vinihate daitye surāḥ sarve 'abhituṣṭuvuḥ|
ṛṣayaśca tapoyuktāḥ puṣpavṛṣṭyaśca petire|| 108.1||
devadundubhayo neduradṛśyāḥ sumahāsvanāḥ|
bhūtānāṃ cābhavaccharma prakṛtisthaṃ jagadbabhau|| 108.2||
jagāmādṛśyatāṃ cakraṃ tataḥ svastābhavan surāḥ|
ṛṣayaścaiva lokāśca daityaṃ taṃ dadṛśurhatam|| 108.3||
asurā api te sarve puradvārāṇi sarvaśaḥ|
pidhāya yatnāt saṃnaddhāḥ prākareṣvavatasthire|| 108.4||
te bhītā muktakeśāśca rajodhvastā bhayārditāḥ|
jīvitaṃ samparīpsantaḥ sthitāḥ prākāragāstadā|| 108.5||
bhagavānapi dīptārcirhaviṣeddha ivānalaḥ|
bhīṣayāno 'asurān sarvān pṛthivīm anvacinvata|| 108.6||
sa bahiḥ sarvato 'anviṣya utpāṭya ca mahīruhān|
praṇaṣṭām iva gāṃ gopaḥ samantādanvacinvata|| 108.7||
parvatān sa tadotpāṭya daityodyānānyacūrṇayat|
ārāmān sa taḍāgāni babhañja ca rarāsa ca|| 108.8||
tato dakṣiṇato gatvā muhūrtaṃ devasattamaḥ|
śaṅkhaṃ parvatam āsādya nanarda jalado yathā|| 108.9||
asurā hyapi te bhītāḥ prākārāntarasaṃsthitāḥ|
avaikṣanta mṛgendraṃ taṃ dhāvantaṃ sarvatodiśaḥ|| 108.10||
so 'api devastadā śaṅkham utpāṭya nagam uttamam|
apaśyat pṛthivīṃ baddhāṃ rakṣyamāṇāṃ ca dānavaiḥ|| 108.11||
sāgarāmbhasi vikṣipya śaṅkhaṃ taṃ parvatottamam|
avadhīddānavān sarvān medinyā ye 'abhirakṣiṇaḥ|| 108.12||
tato vidrāvya nāgendrān pragṛhya pṛthivīṃ balāt|
jagāma daityān saṃdhṛṣya ratnāni ādāya sarvaśaḥ|| 108.13||
sa tāṃ daṃṣṭrāṅkure lagnāṃ vahan bhāti mṛgeśvaraḥ|
viṣāṇalagnāṃ lambavantīṃ mṛṇālīṃ gajarāḍiva|| 108.14||
sa tāṃ sāgaramadhyena vahan bhāti mṛgeśvaraḥ|
varāharūpī kālānte brahmeva vasudhāṃ purā|| 108.15||
sa sāgaraṃ tsam uttīrya bhagavān nandivardhanaḥ|
svasthāne sthāpayāmāsa mahīṃ tāṃ punareva hi|| 108.16||
tataḥ śakrāya lokāṃstrīnadāt sa madhusūdanaḥ|
uvāca rājā tvaṃ no 'adya mitraṃ cāhaṃ tavānagha|| 108.17||
ye 'anye 'api te 'arayaḥ kecidbhaviṣyantyasureśvarāḥ|
teṣām api vadhaṃ ghoraṃ kariṣyāmi na saṃśayaḥ|| 108.18||
tatastam ṛṣayaḥ sarve devatāśca savāsavāḥ|
ūcuḥ svāṃ mūrtim āsthāya yathā pūrvaṃ tathā bhava|| 108.19||
varāha uvāca|
iyaṃ mūrtirmayā devāḥ prāptā paramavarcasā|
na cānayā ratiḥ kācit prāptā me sadṛśī bhuvi|| 108.20||
so 'ahaṃ kaṃcidvihṛtyeha kālaṃ mūrtyānayā sukham|
bhaviṣyāmi punardevaḥ satyam etadbravīmi vaḥ|| 108.21||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā sarve devāḥ savāsavāḥ|
pradakṣiṇam upāvṛtya jagmuḥ sthānāni sarvaśaḥ|| 108.22||
gateṣu devasaṃdheṣu bhagavān nandivardhanaḥ|
vijahāra sukhaṃ tatra hatvā dānavapuṃgavam|| 108.23||
tasya tatropatiṣṭhanta mṛgyo bhūtvā sahasraśaḥ|
vaidikyo 'apsarasaḥ śubhrāstābhiḥ saha rarāma saḥ|| 108.24||
sa tābhirvicaran devo mahātmā nandivardhanaḥ|
reme matto mahānāgo yathāraṇye kareṇubhiḥ|| 108.25||
sa siṃha iva siṃhībhiḥ sārdūla iva connadanan|
rarāma sāgarānūpe airāvata ivāparaḥ|| 108.26||
ramamāṇasya siddhāśca ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
puṣpāṇāṃ rucirā vṛṣṭīḥ pātayanti viyatsthitāḥ|| 108.27||
tuṣṭuvuścāpare nityaṃ cakruścainaṃ pradakṣiṇam|
devadundubhayo nityaṃ sarva evānvavādayan|| 108.28||
nṛtyantyapsarasaścāsya varāhasyāgratastadā|
vādayanti ca gandharvā gāyanti ca mahātmanaḥ|| 108.29||
ramayanto varāhaṃ taṃ devāścendrapurogamāḥ|
yakṣāḥ puṇyajananā ye ca tathā devajanāśca ye|| 108.30||
yātudhānāśca ye kecidbrahmadhānāśca sarvaśaḥ|
manuṣyāḥ paśavaścaiva ṛṣayaścaiva sarvaśaḥ|| 108.31||
rājanyaḥ kṣatriyāḥ sarve nikāyāścaiva sarvaśaḥ|
tatrājagmurnirīkṣanto varāhasyotsavaṃ śubham|| 108.32||
bahvāścaryasamākīrṇaṃ bahvālakṣyaṃ sadaiva ca|
evaṃ tasyābhavadvyāsa varāhasya mahātmanaḥ|
utsavaḥ sumahān divyaḥ pratyahaṃ nandivardhanaḥ|| 108.33||
tasyotsovo 'asau ṛṣisaṃghajuṣṭaḥ sadā suraiḥ siddhajanaiśca juṣṭaḥ|
gandharvayakṣoragarākṣasaiśca vidyādharaiścaiva sahāpsarobhiḥ|| 108.34||
iti skandapurāṇe varāhotsave aṣṭottaraśato .adhyāyaḥ|| 108.108||

skandapurana109
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya kālena mahatā ramataḥ śaktinandana|
bhāryāyāṃ citralekhāyāṃ vṛko nāmābhavat sutaḥ|| 109.1||
sa vṛko balavān nityaṃ vicaran pṛthivīm imām|
nardamāno 'avadhīlloke bhūtāni śataśo mahān|| 109.2||
athāsasāda śailendraṃ himavantaṃ mahāgirim|
gaurīkūṭasamīpe ca kārttikeyālayaṃ śubham|| 109.3||
tam ajānaṃstadābhyetya balenāvinayena ca|
nādayāno drumāñchubhrān ratnahemavibhūṣitān|| 109.4||
sarvartupuṣpaphaladān sarvakāmapradānapi|
śilāmaṇimayāḥ śubhrāḥ śātakumbhamayāstathā|| 109.5||
haritālsamayāścānyāstathā mānaḥśilopālān|
utpāṭyotpāṭya vegena babhañja rūṣito yathā|| 109.6||
sa garjamānaḥ satataṃ gajo matta ivāparaḥ|
babhañja tadvanaṃ śubhraṃ kārttikeyasya dhīmataḥ|| 109.7||
tasya garjitaśabdena vanabhaṅgasvanena ca|
skandasya gaṇapaḥ śūro nirjagāma sa mandirāt|| 109.8||
kokavaktra iti khyato dṛḍhaṃ skandasya vallabhaḥ|
mahātmā balasampanno gatvā vṛkam avaikṣata|| 109.9||
sa taṃ dṛṣṭvā mahākāyaṃ taruṇaṃ priyadarśanam|
jīmūtam iva nardantaṃ kiṃcitprakupitānanam|| 109.10||
uvāca vacanaṃ hṛṣṭaḥ kokavaktro hasanniva|
kasya tvam iha samprāpto bālo devagṛhaṃ śubham|| 109.11||
na jānīṣe kim etat tvaṃ skandasya sumahātmanaḥ|
veśma devaiḥ sagandharvaiḥ sayakṣoragakiṃnaraiḥ|| 109.12||
kṛtaṃ dayitam atyarthaṃ gaṇaiścāpi supūjitam|
kumāro mandaraṃ yātaḥ sarvaiḥ saha gaṇeśvaraiḥ|| 109.13||
rakṣārthaṃ mām iha sthāpya vārayāmi tato hi te|
tuṣṭo 'asmi tava rūpeṇa balena vapuṣā tathā|| 109.14||
upāramasva tena tvāṃ bravīmi sumahābala|
ahaṃ kariṣye yadbhagnaṃ tathaiva punareva hi|| 109.15||
vakṣye devaṃ ca taṃ samyak tvadarthaṃ śūkareśvara|
yathā na kupyate tubhyaṃ prasādaṃ te karoti ca|| 109.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā vṛkaḥ saṃraktalocanaḥ|
uvāca kokavadanam idaṃ mṛgapatistadā|| 109.17||
na bibhemi kumārasya tava vā pāpacetasaḥ|
bale mama kumāro 'asau na tulyaḥ sagaṇeśvaraḥ|| 109.18||
yadvo balaṃ ca darpaśca tat kurudhvam aśaṅkitāḥ|
nāmāvaśeṣam etadvaḥ kartāhaṃ vanam antataḥ|| 109.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa vṛkṣam utpāṭya haimaṃ vaidūryapallavam|
kokavaktrāya cikṣepa nanāda ca yathā vṛṣaḥ|| 109.20||
tataḥ prahasya kokāsyastam evodgṛhya pādapam|
vṛkaṃ taṃ tena saṃkruddhaḥ śirasyabhijaghāna ha|| 109.21||
sa tena suprahāreṇa bhramitvā maṇḍalaṃ mṛgaḥ|
papāta bhūmau niḥsaṃjño yathā śakradhvajo mahān|| 109.22||
tatastaṃ patitaṃ dṛṣṭvā kokāsyaḥ prahasaṃstadā|
babandha pāśairbahubhirveśma caiva praveśayat|| 109.23||
taṃ baddhaṃ patitaṃ dṛṣṭvā sahāyāstasya te mṛgāḥ|
pradrutā sahasā sarve bhayārtā jīvitaiṣiṇaḥ|| 109.24||
athāgāt tena kālena gaṇapairbahubhirvṛtaḥ|
kārttikeyo mayūreṇa kūjamānena sānugaḥ|| 109.25||
tasya tat kathayāmāsa kokavaktro gaṇeśvaraḥ|
vṛkaṃ ca darśayāmāsa pāśairbaddhaṃ mahābalam|| 109.26||
kokavaktra uvāca|
bhagavan varāharūpasya sutaḥ śrīmān vṛkaḥ kila|
hiraṇyākṣo hato yena dānavo devakaṇṭakaḥ|| 109.27||
babhañjāyaṃ suduṣṭātmā sahito 'anyairvanaṃ tava|
tataḥ pāśairmayā baddhaḥ kriyatām asya yat param|| 109.28||
skanda uvāca|
nāyaṃ śakyo mayādyeha moktuṃ mṛgakulādhamaḥ|
mukte vaktavyatā loke bhaviṣyati na saṃśaya|| 29
devo māṃ vakṣyate vyaktaṃ skando bhīto na saṃśayaḥ|
yo mumoca sutaṃ tasya varāhasya kṛtāgasam|| 109.30||
ukto gataścāham adya sthāṇunā paramātmanā|
mā kṣamethā varāhasya tanuṃ tvāsau hvayedyadi|| 109.31||
iyaṃ ca mama tenādya śaktirdattātibhāsvarā|
saṃvarttiketi vikhyātā sarvāstrabalanāśanī|| 109.32||
so 'ayaṃ durātmā durvṛttaḥ sarvalokaprabādhakaḥ|
gṛhyatāṃ vadhyatāṃ caiva kṣipram āviṣkṛtaṃ balāt|| 109.33||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tata enaṃ bahiḥ sarve skandasya gaṇanāyakāḥ|
baddhvā bahuvidhaiḥ pāśairyātayanta sahasraśaḥ|| 109.34||
sa yātyamāno duḥkhārto vilalāpa yathā naraḥ|
nirayastho durācāraḥ karmabhiḥ svaiḥ supāśitaḥ|| 109.35||
taṃ yātyamānaṃ saṃdṛśya nāradaḥ sumahātapāḥ|
gatvā nyavedayat tasya varāhasyāmitātmanaḥ|| 109.36||
eṣa putro vṛkastubhyaṃ baddhaḥ pāśairanekaśaḥ|
yātyate kārttikeyasya kiṃkarairduṣkṛtī yathā|| 109.37||
na nāma tava devasya lokārthāyodyatasya ca|
karoti saṃnatiṃ skando bālabhāvācca roṣataḥ|| 109.38||
athavā svam alaṃ skando manyate balavattaram|
tvattotmanastataḥ putraṃ tava pāśairbabandha ha|| 109.39||
tadyāvadeva taṃ nāsau pramāpayati devapa|
tāvadeva bhavān gatvā vimocayatu mā ciram|| 109.40||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
nāradasya vacaḥ śrutvā varāho nandivardhanaḥ|
jīmūta iva kālānte nanāda rūṣitānanaḥ|| 109.41||
tasya krodhāt tadā vahnirnetrābhyām atidīptimān|
niścakrāma jagat sarvaṃ saṃharanniva tejasā|| 109.42||
utthāya cāsanāddevaḥ sahasaivonnirīkṣaṇaḥ|
pratasthe śikharaṃ divyaṃ gauryā mṛgapatiḥ svayam|| 109.43||
sa kampayan mahīṃ sarvāṃ stūyamāno mahātmabhiḥ|
utpātānutthitān paśyan jagāmāvinivāritaḥ|| 109.44||
gacchatastasya devasya panthānaṃ bhujago 'acchinat|
daṃṣṭrā ca vṛkṣam āpatya papāta dharaṇītale|| 109.45||
rudhiraṃ cāsravadvaktrāddhṛdayaṃ ca pravepata|
bhayaṃ cāsyābhavat tatra vego yenābhihanyate|| 109.46||
vāyavaḥ pratilomāśca urasā cāpatadbhuvi|
snehaścāsya priyāṃ smṛtvā tadātyartham ajāyata|| 109.47||
etāṃścānyān subahuśa utpātān bhayasūcakān|
anādṛtya mṛgendro 'asau jagāmaiva mahābalaḥ|| 109.48||
taṃ prasthitam abhiprekṣya nimittāni ca suvrata|
pūjāṃ sajjām akurvante delavoke divaukasaḥ|| 109.49||
sa siddhasaṃghairanugamyamāno yakṣaiśca gandharvamahoragaiśca|
rakṣogaṇaiścāraṇakiṃnaraiśca jagāma gaurīśikharaṃ mahātmā|| 109.50||
iti skandapurāṇe vṛkabandho nāma navottaraśato .adhyāyaḥ|| 109.109||

skandapurana110
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vinirgamya kumāro 'api ramyāt svabhavanāt tadā|
rarāma gaṇapaiḥ sārdhaṃ krīḍanairbahubhiḥ śubhaiḥ|| 110.1||
ānayāmāsa taṃ cāpi varāhasya sutaṃ prabhuḥ|
vṛkaṃ vimucya pāśebhya utsasarja hasan vibhuḥ|| 110.2||
utsṛṣṭaṃ dhāvamānaṃ ca punarjagrāha vegitam|
punarevotsṛjaccainaṃ jagrāha ca punaḥ punaḥ|
evaṃ rarāma tenāsau varāho 'abhyāgamacca tam|| 110.3||
śilāṃ gṛhītvā mahatīṃ saṃkruddho 'antakasaṃnibhaḥ|
cikṣepa kārttikeyāya nādayan jalado yathā|| 110.4||
tām āpatantīṃ bahudhā nadantīṃ vihāyasā mṛtyusamānarūpām|
jagrāha vegena mahātivegāṃ kokāmukhaḥ prajvalitām ivolkām|| 110.5||
tataścakraṃ sahasrāraṃ yugāntāgnisamaprabham|
vināyakasyāvyagrāya gaṇāya vyasṛjat prabhuḥ|| 110.6||
tadantakapratīkāśaṃ cakraṃ sarvasurāriham|
viveśa sagaṇastūrṇaṃ tatastadvinyavartata|| 110.7||
tannivṛttaṃ punaścakram akṛtvā kāryam ujjvalam|
na jagrāha tadā viṣṇuravamene ca tat tadā|| 110.8||
tat tadānarcitaṃ tena cakraṃ dānavaghātinā|
viṣṇunā prayayau kṣipraṃ svam eva bhavanaṃ prati|| 110.9||
tasmiṃścakre tadā yāte bhagavān nandivardhanaḥ|
vṛkṣam utpāṭya vegena kumāram abhijaghnivān|| 110.10||
agaṇya taṃ prahāraṃ tu bhagavānanalātmajaḥ|
śaktiṃ saṃvarttikāṃ krodhāccikṣepa ca nanāda ca|| 110.11||
sā dahantīva tejāṃsi nadantī bahudhā tadā|
hantuṃ varāhaṃ prayayau śaktirdivya ivāśugaḥ|| 110.12||
tām āpamantīṃ vegena bhagavān nandivardhanaḥ|
jaghānāstrairbahuvidhairnādayan siṃharāḍiva|| 110.13||
tāni sā bhasmasāt kṛtvā śaktiḥ saṃvarttikā śubhā|
viveśa hṛdayaṃ tasya kāminīva dṛḍhaṃ priyā|| 110.14||
sa tayā bhinnahṛdayo yogena parameṇa ha|
yogīva dehaṃ taṃ tyaktvā dehenānyena tasthivān|| 110.15||
so 'anyaddehaṃ samāsthāya paurāṇaṃ surasattamaḥ|
devaiḥ sarvaiḥ parivṛto jagāma bhavamandiram|| 110.16||
tatrāpaśyanmahādevaṃ jaṭāmukuṭadhāriṇam|
candralekhāṃśujālaughanirastatimirotkaram|| 110.17||
bhadrapīṭhe samāsīnaṃ kāñcane maṇimūṣaṇe|
bhrājamānaṃ śriyātyarthaṃ pārvatyā pārśvasṃsthayā|| 110.18||
gaṇaiśca vividhākārairbahubhiḥ kāmarūpibhiḥ|
nṛttagītapriyairnityaṃ samantāt parivāritam|| 110.19||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā śaṃkaraṃ viṣṇuḥ prasannenāntarātmanā|
tuṣṭāva vividhaiḥ stotrairidaṃ covāca susvaram|| 110.20||
vārāhaṃ rūpam āsthāya tvattejobṛṃhitena me|
raṇe vikramya bhagavan hiraṇyākṣo niṣūditaḥ|| 110.21||
tvaṃ deva kāraṇaṃ nityaṃ sambhūteḥ pralayasya ca|
tvayā sarvam idaṃ vyāptaṃ jagadavyaktamūrtinā|| 110.22||
tvatprasādena deveśa brahmāhaṃ śakra eva ca|
pūjyāḥ sma loke satataṃ tathaivānye divaukasaḥ|| 110.23||
tvayi prīte mahādeva sarve prītā vayaṃ prabho|
tvayi kruddhe vināśo no bhavitā nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 110.24||
stuvantam evaṃ bhagavān viṣṇuṃ candrārdhaśekharaḥ|
sahasrasūryatejaskaḥ prītaḥ provāca śaṃkaraḥ|| 110.25||
bhaktyā tuṣṭo 'asmi te viṣṇo devakāryodyamena ca|
varaṃ varaya bhadraṃ te yaste manasi vartate|| 110.26||
viṣṇuruvāca|
yadi tuṣṭo 'asi no deva yadi deyo varaśca naḥ|
yat tat pāpaharaṃ divyaṃ vratam ādeṣṭum arhasi|| 110.27||
yadāśritya vayaṃ sarve saśakrāḥ sārvakāmikam|
yuddhe jeṣyāma daiteyān duḥkhaśokavivarjitāḥ|| 110.28||
devadeva uvāca|
hanta vaḥ kathayiṣyāmi guhyam etat sanātanam|
vrataṃ pāśupataṃ divyaṃ yena kāmānavāpsyatha|| 110.29||
ityuktvā devadeveśo devānāṃ hitakāmyayā|
yayau divam athāmantrya devīṃ girivarātmajām|| 110.30||
atha himagiritulyacārumūrti vṛṣabhavaraṃ bhagavāṃstadādhirūḍhaḥ|
suragaṇasahitaḥ prabhuḥ sumeruṃ vratam upadeṣṭumanā jagāma śarvaḥ|| 110.31||
iti skandapurāṇe hiraṇyākṣavadhe
varāharūpasaṃhāre devadevasya devalokagamanaṃ nāma
daśottaraśato .adhyāyaḥ|| 110.110||

skandapurana111
vyāsa uvāca|
gate divaṃ mahādeve vratam ādeṣṭum uttamam|
ekākinī mahādevī kiṃ cakre tadanantaram|| 111.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
gate divaṃ mahādeve devīṃ girivarātmajām|
upatasthurmahābhāgā devyo lokasya mātaraḥ|| 111.2|
bharatasya sutāgnestu mālinītyabhiviśrutā|
śucāvatī ca devasya parjanyasya sutāvyayā|| 111.3||
sāvitrī devamātā ca gāyatrī durgayā saha|
śrīḥ kīrtiścaiva lakṣmīśca dhṛtiḥ prajñā tathaiva ca|| 111.4||
khyātirditirdanuścaiva aditiḥ siṃhikā khaśā|
rākā kuhūḥ sinīvālī tathaivānumatiḥ śubhā|| 111.5||
gaṅgā sarasvatī caiva tathānyāḥ saritaḥ śubhāḥ|
ṛṣīṇāṃ caiva yāḥ patnyo devānāṃ yakṣarakṣasām|
uragāṇāṃ khagānāṃ ca gandharvāṇāṃ tathaiva ca|| 111.6||
etāḥ sarvāstathāgamya namaskṛtya ca pārvatīm|
papracchuḥ sarvadharmajñā dharmaṃ dharmārthasaṃśritāḥ|| 111.7||
kena dharmeṇa deveśe tapasā vā śubhānane|
mumahat prāpyate puṇyaṃ kiṃ cākṣayyaṃ prakīrtitam|| 111.8||
devyuvāca|
yusmākaṃ tu hitārthāya lokānāṃ caiva suvratāḥ|
kathayiṣyāmyahaṃ dharmaṃ yathāvadanupūrvaśaḥ|| 111.9||
annadānāt paraṃ dānaṃ naiva kiṃciddhi vidyate|
annādbhavanti bhūtāni tasmāt tadadhikaṃ smṛtam|| 111.10||
annaṃ yastu susaṃskṛtya prayaccheta dvijātaye|
sa sarvakāmān āpnoti pūjyate ca triviṣṭape|| 111.11||
mayūrahaṃsayuktena sarvakāmasamṛddhinā|
vimānenārkabhāsena annado yāti vai divam|| 111.12||
yadi mānuṣyam āyāti kadācit sa narottamaḥ|
dhanadhānyasamākīrṇaḥ kulīnaḥ syācca rūpavān|| 111.13||
yathāśakti tu yo dadyāddivase divase naraḥ|
sa tena karmaṇāpnoti prajāpatisalokatām|| 111.14||
kadācidapi yo dadyādannaṃ vprāya saṃskṛtam|
tasyāpi tacchataguṇaṃ sahasraguṇam eva ca|| 111.15||
upatiṣṭhati lokeṣu ihāpi ca sukhī bhavet|
avadhūtam avajñātam asatkṛtam athāpi ca|| 111.16||
annaṃ pradadyādyo devyo yādṛśaṃ tādṛśaṃ śubhāḥ|
tasyāpi narake ghore yātyamānasya rākṣasaiḥ|| 111.17||
upatiṣṭheta bahudhā tṛptiryenāsya jāyate|
yadi mānuṣyam āyāti kadācit sa naraḥ punaḥ|| 111.18||
mleccheṣu bhogī bhavati ramate ca yathāmaraḥ|
annem evaṃ viśiṣṭaṃ hi tasmānna paramaṃ bhuvi|| 111.19||
annaṃ prajāpatiḥ proktaṃ sa ca saṃvatsaro mataḥ|
saṃvatasaraśca yajño 'asau yajñe sarvaṃ pratiṣṭhitam|| 111.20||
tasmādbhavanti bhūtāni sthāvarāṇi carāṇi ca|
tasmādannaṃ viśiṣṭhaṃ tu sarvebhya iti vai śrutiḥ|| 111.21||
annadānāt paraṃ dānaṃ naiva kiṃciddhi vidyate|
annādbhavanti bhūtāni tasmāt tadvai praśasyate|| 111.22||
sugandhāḥ śītalāścāpo rasairdivyaiḥ samanvitāḥ|
yaḥ prayacchati viprebhyastasya dānaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 111.23||
vimānaṃ sūryasaṃkāśam apsarogaṇanāditam|
so 'adhiruhya divaṃ yāti varuṇasya salokatām|| 111.24||
tatrāsāvayutānyaṣṭāvuṣitvā devavat sukhī|
kule mahatyasaṃkīrṇo jāyate dhanadhānyavān|| 111.25||
āpāṃ tu pūrṇaṃ yo bhāṇḍaṃ brāhmaṇāya prayacchati|
rasāstasyopatiṣṭhanti pūjyate ca divaṃ gataḥ|| 111.26||
bhājanāni ca yo dadyāt supūrṇāni śubhānanāḥ|
bhājanaṃ syāt sa bhogānāṃ tārayecca pitR̥n bhayāt|| 111.27||
taḍāgaṃ yastu kurvīta apāṃ devyaḥ samṛddhimat|
apaḥ pibanti vai yatra sarve jantava eva ca|| 111.28||
tārayitvā ca sa pitR̥ṃstathaiva ca pitāmahān|
prapitāmahāṃśca lokeṣu kamikeṣu vihaṃgamaḥ|| 111.29||
carate devavaddevyo varṣāyutaśātāni ṣaṭ|
punaśca mānuṣe loke sarvarogavivarjitaḥ|| 111.30||
bhogī bhavati bhogānāṃ rājamātraśca jāyate|
dātā yajyā ca balavān suprabhaḥ priyadarśanaḥ|| 111.31||
avaṭaṃ yo naraḥ kuryādapāṃ pūrṇaṃ śucismitāḥ|
dadyācca brāhmaṇebhyastaṃ bhojayitvā yathārthavat|| 111.32||
aṣṭābhiśca vicitrābhiḥ patākābhiralaṃkṛtam|
dhvajena vaijayantyā ca puṣpaiśca samalaṃkṛtam|| 111.33||
sa tārayitvā tu pitR̥n vimānena narottamaḥ|
yātyapsaropagītena varuṇasya salokatām|| 111.34||
hiraṇyaṃ hema bhūmiṃ vā tilān ratnāni vāpi yaḥ|
pradadyāt sarvabhūtebhyastasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu|| 111.35||
sa vimānena mahatā sarvalokasamanvitaḥ|
indrasya lokaṃ saṃprāpya modate vibudho yathā|| 111.36||
tataścyutaśca dharmātmā sarvakāmasamṛddhimān|
kule mahati loke 'asau jāyate subhagaśca ha|| 111.37||
yastu vṛkṣaṃ prakurute chāyāpuṣpaphalopagam|
pathi devyo naraḥ somye sa tārayati vai pitR̥n|| 111.38||
tathaiva dattvā viprebhyo niṣkrīya ca punarnaraḥ|
sa yat phalam avāpnoti tacchṛṇudhvaṃ mahāprabhāḥ|| 111.39||
yāvadvṛkṣasya puṣpāṇi upayuñjanti dehinaḥ|
phalāni caiva bhakṣyante jantubhiḥ phalitasya tu|| 111.40||
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi tārayitvā pitR̥nnapi|
somalokaṃ samāsādya so 'amṛtaṃ phalam āpnuyāt|| 111.41||
phalāni yaḥ prayaccheta brāhmaṇebhyaḥ samāhitaḥ|
phalānāṃ sa tu bhāgī syādbahūnāṃ subhagaśca ha|| 111.42||
kāṣṭhāni yaḥ prayaccheta hemante narasattamaḥ|
brāhmaṇebhyastadā devyaḥ so 'agnilokaṃ samaśnute|| 111.43||
bhājanaṃ yaḥ prayaccheta haimaṃ ratnavibhūṣitam|
so 'apsaraḥśatasaṃkīrṇe vimāne divi modate|| 111.44||
rājataṃ yaḥ prayaccheta viprebhyo bhājanaṃ śubhāḥ|
sa gāndharvapadaṃ prāpya urvaśyā saha modate|| 111.45||
tāmraṃ yo bhājanaṃ dadyādbrāhmaṇebhyo viśeṣataḥ|
sa bhavedyakṣarājasya yakṣo balasamanvitaḥ|| 111.46||
gṛhaṃ yastu prayaccheta sarvakāmasamṛddhimat|
sa lokaṃ brahmaṇaḥ prāpya sarvakāmairniṣevyate|| 111.47||
sarvakoṭīḥ sa tatroṣya catasrastena karmaṇā|
gṛhamedhī yadā dātā bhogavāṃścaiva jāyate|| 111.48||
oṣadhīryaḥ prayaccheta dhānyāni vividhāni ca|
sa sarvakāmasaṃmṛṣṭaṃ somalokaṃ samaśnute|| 111.49||
tatra varṣasahasrāṇi sapta sthitvā punarnaraḥ|
iha sarvadhanopeto bhogāvānabhijāyate|| 111.50||
yastu kṣetraṃ prayaccheta niṣpannaṃ phalavat punaḥ|
sa tu kṣetrapatirbhūtvā prājāpatyaṃ samaśnute|| 111.51||
yastu bhūmiṃ prayaccheta brahmaṇāya mahātmane|
sa sarvalokeṣu sukhī vimānena suvarcasā|| 111.52||
bahūnyabdasahasrāṇi carate kāmarūpavān|
yaddhi mānuṣyam āyāti sa naraḥ kālaparyayāt|| 111.53||
tatra kāmaduhā tasya mahī bhavati sarvaśaḥ|
yastu vastraṃ prayaccheta brāhmaṇāya mahāyaśāḥ|| 111.54||
sa lokaṃ prāpya vairājaṃ varṣakoṭiṃ sukhaṃ vaset|
āsanaṃ yaḥ prayaccheta saṃvītaṃ brāhmaṇāya vai|| 111.55||
sa rājyasthānam āpnoti svargaṃ cāpnoti vijvaraḥ|
yastu śayyāṃ prayaccheta svāstīrṇāṃ narasattamaḥ|| 111.56||
sa tu bhāryāḥ priyā devyo bahvīrbhaktāḥ samaśnute|
yastu kanyāṃ prayaccheta brāhmaṇāya svalaṃkṛtām|| 111.57||
sa gatvā pitṛlokaṃ vai varṣāyutaśataṃ vaset|
iha cāpi punarjātaḥ sarvakāmasamanvitaḥ|| 111.58||
bharyāḥ prāpnoti bhaktāśca prajāvāṃścopajāyate|
aśvaṃ yastu prayaccheta hemacitraṃ sulakṣaṇam|| 111.59||
sa tena karmaṇā devyo gāndharvaṃ lokam aśnute|
ratham aśvaṃ gajaṃ dāsīṃ kanyāṃ gṛham athāpi ca|| 111.60||
bhūmiṃ ca yaḥ prayaccheta sa rājā bhuvi jāyate|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 111.61||
vidhinā mantrayuktena tasya dharmaphalaṃ mahat|
sarvakāmadughā sāsya dhenurbhūtvopatiṣṭhati|| 111.62||
jaladhenuṃ ca yo dadyāt tasya dānaphalaṃ mahat|
prāpāṃ śubhāṃ taḍāgaṃ vā kūpaṃ vāpi supuṣkalam|| 111.63||
kṛtvā kumbhān susaṃpūrṇān gandhamālyairalaṃkṛtān|
puṣpaiśca vivadhākārairabhyarcya dvijasattamān|| 111.64||
bhakṣyabhojyaiḥ suptṛptāṃstāṃstilapātrāṇi dāpayet|
dakṣiṇāṃ puṣkalāṃ dadyāt tebhyastāṃ sparśayet tataḥ|| 111.65||
āpaḥ śivāśca saumyāśca tarpayantu pitR̥n mama|
kāmagāḥ kāmadātāro bhavantu pitaraḥ sadā|| 111.66||
evaṃ dattvā tu tāṃ dhenuṃ punaḥ krītvā ca vai tadā|
vāhayet tat prapāṃ devyo brahmalokasamarpaṇīm|| 111.67||
tilapātrāṇi dattvā ca tathā vastrayugaṃ navam|
suvarṇasya ca sāṃnidhyaṃ phalāni vividhāni ca|| 111.68||
tato dadyācchuciḥ snāto brāhmaṇebhyo yathāvidhi|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 111.69||
ghṛtaṃ gāvaḥ prasūyante ghṛtaṃ bhūmyāṃ pratiṣṭhitam|
ghṛtam agniśca devāśca ghṛtaṃ me saṃpradīyatām|| 111.70||
evaṃ vidhānato dattvā brahmalokam avāpnuyāt|
yo naro gāṃ prayaccheta savatsāṃ kāṃsyadohanīm|| 111.71||
hemaśṛṅgīṃ rūpyakhurāṃ dukūlakṣaumavāsitām|
śayyāstaraṇasaṃpannāṃ bahupuṣpaphalairyutām|| 111.72||
brāhmaṇāṃstarpayitvā tu gandhamālyairalaṃkṛtām|
dānakāle tatastasyāḥ surā gātrāṇi saṃśritāḥ|| 111.73||
brahmā tasyāḥ sthito mūrdhni śakro 'apānaṃ samāśritaḥ|
candrādityau ca netrasthau ghrāṇe vāyuḥ pratiṣṭhitaḥ|| 111.74||
mukhaṃ tasyāḥ śrito vahnirjihvāṃ somaḥ svayaṃ prabhuḥ|
karṇayostu diśaḥ sarvāḥ śirā rudrāḥ samāśritāḥ|| 111.75||
pādayorlokapālāśca sarve 'asthīni ca parvatāḥ|
samudrāḥ sapta jaṭhare grīvāyāṃ tapanāḥ śritāḥ|| 111.76||
sāsnāṃ gaṅgā saricchreṣṭhā pārśvayorvasavaḥ śubhāḥ|
prajāpatirupasthaśca mūtraṃ tīrthāni sarvaśaḥ|| 111.77||
purīṣaṃ śrīrabhūt tasyā nāgāścāstrāṇi sarvaśaḥ|
sādhyā viśve 'atha lokāśca puccham āśritya saṃsthitāḥ|| 111.78||
mantrā yajñāśca dānāni yamāśca ṛṣibhiḥ saha|
nakṣatrāṇi grahāścaiva tārārūpāṇi yāni ca|| 111.79||
gāyatrī caiva triṣṭup ca jagatī paṅktireva ca|
anuṣṭubṛgyajuścaiva sāmāni ātharvaṇaṃ tathā|| 111.80||
lokasya mātaraścaiva meghā varṣam athāpi ca|
dharmastārāyaṇaścaiva bhūtāni saritastathā|| 111.81||
romakūpāni saṃśritya tasyā devā vyavasthitāḥ|
yakṣāśca rākṣasāścaiva piśācāḥ pakṣibhiḥ saha|| 111.82||
yajñāśca dakṣiṇāścaiva tathā cāpsarasaḥ śubhāḥ|
gandharvāśca mahātmāno ye cānye 'apyevamādayaḥ|| 111.83||
tasyā viṣāṇayorvyāsa sarva eva samāśritāḥ|
phalāni yajñadānānāṃ gatayaśca pṛthagvidhāḥ|| 111.84||
vatsaṃ samāśritāḥ sarve sarvaṃ devamayaṃ śubham|
devairadhyāsitāṃ tāṃ tu sarvalokanamaskṛtam|| 111.85||
viprebhyo mantravaddhaste pradadyāt susamāhitaḥ|
kuśān suvarṇaṃ bījāni tilān siddhārthakāṃstathā|| 111.86||
pradadyādgāṃ tato 'adbhistu mantreṇānena suvrata|
sarvadevamayīṃ dogdhrīṃ sarvalokamayīṃ tathā|| 111.87||
sarvalokanimittāya sarvalokahitāya ca|
prayacchāmi mahāsattvām akṣayāya śubhām iti|| 111.88||
evaṃ sa dattvā tāṃ gāṃ tu yatra yatra prajāyate|
tatra tatra gatā sā taṃ jantuṃ tārayate bhayāt|| 111.89||
sarvakāmaduhā caiva sarvalokapradā tathā|
sarvajñānapradā caiva sarvayajñaphalā tathā|| 111.90||
sarvā lokān tayā gatvā ramate ca yathāmaraḥ|
iha jātaśca tām eva kāmagāṃ saṃprapadyate|| 111.91||
sa tayā mānuṣo jāto gosahasrī mahābalaḥ|
rūpavān dhanavāṃścaiva bahuputraśca jāyate|| 111.92||
prasūyamānāṃ yo gāṃ tu dadyādubhayatomukhīm|
yathoktena vidhānena sa jātismaratāṃ labhet|| 111.93||
yastu gāṃ saṃprayaccheta brāhmaṇebhyo yathātatham|
tam apyasau bhayārthemyastrāyate narakādapi|| 111.94||
kṛṣṇājinaṃ ca yo dadyādvratine brahmacāriṇe|
pṛthivīphalam āpnoti yogaścāsya pravartate|| 111.95||
yogibhyo brahmacāribhyo brāhmaṇebhyo yatātmavān|
yaḥ prayacchedāvasathaṃ so 'aśvamedhaphalaṃ labhet|| 111.96||
āptoryāmaṃ pauṇḍarīkaṃ gosahasraṃ ca vindati|
smṛtiṃ ca paramāṃ labdhvā yogam āpnoti suvratāḥ|| 111.97||
kamaṇḍaluṃ tu yo dadyādbrāhmaṇāya narottamaḥ|
sa tena karmaṇā devyo dharmanityatvam āpnute|| 111.98||
vyādhitaṃ yastu viprarṣe dīnaṃ mūḍham acetasam|
uddhareta yathāśaktyā sa mucyedbrahmahatyayā|| 111.99||
yaḥ suvarṇaṃ prayaccheta daridrāya dvijātaye|
daśānām aśamedhānāṃ phalaṃ prāpnoti devatāḥ|| 111.100||
yaścaivemāni sarvāṇi dānānyuktāni kṛtsnaśaḥ|
dadāti yugapaddevyaḥ sa pṛthvyām ekarāḍbhavet|| 111.101||
idaṃ yaḥ śṛṇuyānnityaṃ dadyāccaiva svaśaktitaḥ|
paṭheta ca mahābhāgāḥ so 'api gacchet triviṣṭapam|| 111.102||
iti skandapurāṇe ekādaśottaraśato .adhyāyaḥ|| 111.111||

skandapurana112
devyuvāca|
devyāḥ śṛṇuta bhūyo 'api yathā dānaṃ vinā śubhāḥ|
ayam evopavāsena yathā dharmo 'abhilabhyate|| 112.1||
ekabhaktena yo devyo māsaṃ mārgaśiraṃ kṣapet|
sa tena karmaṇā devyo gomān bhavati nityaśaḥ|| 112.2||
pauṣamāsena putrāṃśca bahūn āpnoti dhārmikān|
māghamāse ca kurvāṇo bhūyaḥ prāpnoti vai priyāḥ|| 112.3||
ekabhaktaṃ tu kurvāṇaḥ phālgune māsi nityaśaḥ|
strīṣu saubhāgyam āpnoti striyaśca paramapriyāḥ|| 112.4||
yaḥ kṣapedekabhaktena caitramāsaṃ narottamaḥ|
dhanadhānyasamṛddhe sa kule jāyeta rūpavān|| 112.5||
vaiśākhaṃ yaḥ kṣapenmāsam ekabhaktena mānavaḥ|
yāti sa śreṣṭhānāṃ loke pūjito dhanavānapi|| 112.6||
jyeṣṭhamūlaṃ tu yo māsam ekabhaktaṃ samācaret|
bhrātR̥ṇāṃ bhavati jyeṣṭho bhogaṃ prāpnoti puṣkalam|| 112.7||
āṣāḍhaṃ cāpi yo māsam ekabhaktaṃ samācaret|
sa rājño mānyatāṃ prāpya kāmān āpnoti puṣkalān|| 112.8||
śravaṇe cāpi yo māse tathā caivācarennaraḥ|
senāpatyaṃ sa saṃprāpya balavānabhijāyate|| 112.9||
yastu bhādrapadaṃ māsam ekabhaktaṃ samācaret|
sa tena karmaṇā devyo dhanavānabhijāyate|| 112.10||
yo 'api cāśvayujaṃ māsam ekabhaktena tiṣṭhati|
vāṇijyaṃ phalate tasya kṛṣiḥ paśugaṇāstathā|| 112.11||
kārttikaṃ tvapi yo māsam ekabhaktena tiṣṭhati|
so 'aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya vahniloke mahīyate|| 112.12||
yaḥ kṣapedekabhaktena yāvajjīvaṃ narottamaḥ|
vimānenārkavarṇena śakralokaṃ sa gacchati| 13||
saṃvatsaraṃ tu yaḥ pūrṇam ekabhaktena tiṣṭhati|
sa pārthivasamo bhūtvā mahīṃ pāti mahendravat|| 112.14||
ahorātraṃ tūpavāsaṃ kuryādekaṃ narottamaḥ|
daśānāṃ sa suvarṇānāṃ phalaṃ prāpnoti śobhitam|| 112.15||
māse māse tvahorātraṃ yaḥ karoti narottamaḥ|
sa tena karmaṇā śuddho vidvān bhavati dhārmikaḥ|| 112.16||
caturdaśīm aṣṭamīṃ ca pakṣayorubhayorapi|
ahorātraṃ kṣapedyastu saṃvatsaram aśeṣataḥ|| 112.17||
sa tena karmaṇā yuktaḥ sarvapāpavivarjitaḥ|
na yāti narakaṃ devyo yamaṃ ca na sa paśyati|| 112.18||
māse māse ca yaḥ kuryāt trirātrakṣapaṇaṃ budhaḥ|
kauberaṃ lokam āsādya sa vindeta paramaṃ sukham|| 112.19||
caturthe 'ahani yo bhuṅkte prayatātmā śucirnaraḥ|
gāndharvaṃ sa padaṃ prāpya modate śakravaddivi|| 112.20||
pañcame 'ahani yo bhuṅkte pratimāsam atandritaḥ|
vāyulokaṃ samāsādya svargalokaṃ sa gacchati|| 112.21||
yo bhuṅkte divase ṣaṣṭhe nityaṃ niyamam āsthitaḥ|
vāruṇaṃ lokam āsādya so 'api vindenmahat padam|| 112.22||
saptame 'ahani yo bhuṅkte jitadvandvo dṛḍhavrataḥ|
ādityalokam āsādya so 'api vindenmahat padam|| 112.23||
aṣṭame caiva yo bhuṅkte divase mānavaḥ śuciḥ|
vaiṣṇavaṃ lokam āsādya sa bhavet paramadyutiḥ|| 112.24||
navame 'ahani yo bhuṅkte naro niyamam āsthitaḥ|
sa vasūnāṃ priyo bhūtvā carate vasubhiḥ saha|| 112.25||
daśame 'ahani bhuktvā tu daśāhasya phalaṃ labhet|
aśvibhyāṃ ca samo bhūtvā sūryavajjvalate sadā|| 112.26||
mānuṣyaṃ ca punaḥ prāpya daśabhāryā labhate saḥ|
suvarṇam akṣayaṃ caiva na cākāle mriyate saḥ|| 112.27||
ekādaśe tu yo bhuṅkte divase mānavaḥ śuciḥ|
ekadaśyāḥ phalaṃ prāpya sa rudragaṇatāṃ labhet|| 112.28||
sthitvā tatra śatānyaṣṭāvatisaukhyasamanvitaḥ|
brāhmaṇatvam anuprāpya yajvā sa iha jāyate|| 112.29||
dvādaśe divase yastu devyo bhuṅkte sadā naraḥ|
dvādaśāhaṃ sa saṃprāpya śakralokam avāpnuyāt|| 112.30||
tatroṣya sa sukhaṃ bhūya iha jāto narottamaḥ|
rājā vā rājamātro vā dhanvā vā sumahān bhavet|| 112.31||
trayodaśe tu yo nityam aśnāti divase naraḥ|
vaset sa bhārgavasthānaṃ prāpya divyasukhānvitaḥ|| 112.32||
atha cenmānuṣo bhūyaḥ sa naro jāyate śubhāḥ|
dhanadhānyasamākīrṇe jāyate satkule śubhaḥ|| 112.33||
caturdaśa tu yo nityaṃ divasāni kṣapennaraḥ|
tauṣitaṃ lokam āsādya bhavedgaṇapatirvaraḥ|| 112.34||
ardhamāsaṃ kṣapedyastu nityam eva hyatandritaḥ|
devarājena tulyo 'asau bhūtvā svarge 'avatiṣṭhati|| 112.35||
iha rājā mahān bhūmau bhūya evābhijāyate|
yastu māsaṃ kṣapeddhīro jitakrodho jitendriyaḥ|| 112.36||
vimānena sa divyena apsarobhiḥ samāvṛtaḥ|
pūjyamāno yathā devaḥ stūyamānaśca sarvaśaḥ|| 112.37||
jvalan ādityasaṃkāśo nityaṃ sukham upāśnute|
sarvalokeṣu vasate bahūnyabdāyutāni tu|| 112.38||
tato brahmasadaṃ prāpy brahmaṇā sa supūjitaḥ|
brahmaloke nivasate yathā brahmā narottamaḥ|| 112.39||
atha cet punarāyāti brāhmaṇo bhavatīśvaraḥ|
yogaṃ ca tatra labhate yogaiśvaryaṃ samaśnute|| 112.40||
yogīśaḥ sa tato bhūtvā śambhorgaṇapatirbhavet|
sarveṣāṃ copavāsānāṃ vidhiṃ paramapuṇyadam|| 112.41||
devyaḥ śṛṇudhvaṃ matto 'anyaṃ yathāvadanupūrvaśaḥ|
snātaḥ śucirathācānto hutāgniḥ susamāhitaḥ|| 112.42||
dīkṣayitvā tathātmānam upavāsaṃ caredbudhaḥ|
snāyāt triṣavaṇaṃ caiva juhuyādagnim eva ca|| 112.43||
vāgyato 'akrodhano dānto dhārmikaḥ satyavāgghṛṇī|
japan sadaiva gāyatrīṃ pavitrāṇi ca nityaśaḥ|| 112.44||
rudrānatha gaṇān vāpi rātrau ca sthaṇḍileśayaḥ|
kuśān āstīrya vidhivat strīśūdraiḥ parivarjitaḥ|| 112.45||
samaśnīyāt tato devyo vītaśoko vimatsaraḥ|
yāvantyahāni tiṣṭheta tāvadviprāṃstu bhojayet|| 112.46||
tataḥ pūrṇe tu kāle vai brāhmaṇānāṃ śataṃ varam|
sahasram athavā śaktyā pūjayitvā tu sarvaśaḥ|| 112.47||
haviṣyaṃ bhojanaṃ dattvā gāśca vāsāṃsi ca kramāt|
suvarṇaṃ tilapātraṃ ca ekaikasya pradāpayet|
tataqstat phalam āpnoti yadanyairdurlabhaṃ vrataiḥ|| 112.48||
vṛṣabhaṃ yastu nīlāṅgam utsṛjeta narottamaḥ|
anyaṃ vāpi mahābhāgāḥ sa pitR̥ṃstārayennaraḥ|| 112.49||
yāvanti tasya romāṇi vṛṣabhasya mahātmanaḥ|
tāvatnyeva sahasrāṇi varṣāṇāṃ divi modate|| 112.50||
tilapātrāṇi yo dadyādviprebhyaḥ śuddhamānasaḥ|
amāvāsyāṃ samāsādya kṛṣṇānāṃ susamāhitaḥ|| 112.51||
sa pitR̥ṃstarpayitvā tu akṣayaṃ narapuṃgavaḥ|
pitṛlokaṃ samāpnoti ciraṃ ca sukham aśnute|| 112.52||
upavāsavidhistveṣa kathito me śubhānanāḥ|
cāndrāyaṇavidhiṃ bhūyaḥ śṛṇudhvaṃ susamāhitāḥ|| 112.53||
yastu cāndrāyaṇaṃ kuryādyathoktaṃ susamāhitaḥ|
sa somalokam āsādya somena samatāṃ vrajet|| 112.54||
prājāpatyaṃ tu yaḥ kuryādekaśo bahuśo 'api vā|
prajāpatisamo bhūtvā tasya loke mahīyate|| 112.55||
yastu sāntapanaṃ kṛcchraṃ karoti narasattamaḥ|
ātmānam uddharet kṛcchrāt so 'agnilokaṃ ca gacchati|| 112.56||
mahāsāntapanaṃ yaśca karoti sumahāmanāḥ|
sarvajñatām avāpnoti brahmalokam ca vindati|| 112.57||
tulāpuruṣakaṃ yaśca kurute dvijasattamaḥ|
sa muktaḥ sarvapāpaistu gācheta divam ūrjitaḥ|| 112.58||
atikṛcchreṇa tu naraḥ śarvasya bhavanaṃ vrajet|
kṛcchrātikṛcchreṇa tathā gāṇapatyam avāpnuyāt|| 112.59||
yastu sarvāṇi kṛcchrāṇi kurute narasattamaḥ|
sa yaṃ prārthayate kāmaṃ tam eva samupāśnute|| 112.60||
yasya kasyacideteṣāṃ kartā syāt susamāhitaḥ|
sa tena śuddho bhavati devatvaṃ cāpi vindati|| 112.61||
payobhakṣastu yo nityaṃ naraḥ saṃvatsaraṃ vaset|
yāvakaṃ copayuñjāno gomūtreṇābhisaṃskṛtam|| 112.62||
piṇyākaphalabhakṣo vā akṣāralavaṇo 'api vā|
so 'aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya brahmalokaṃ samaśnute|| 112.63||
sarvapāpavinirmukto vimuktaḥ sarvabandhanaiḥ|
vimānenārkavarṇena brahmavaccarate ca saḥ|| 112.64||
yastvetānyeva sarvāṇi vyastāni narasattamaḥ|
yāvaducchvāsam āśete mahātmā naṣṭakilbiṣaḥ|| 112.65||
sa lokān vā mahāsattvo yatheṣṭān mokṣam eva vā|
aiśvaryaṃ vā mahat prāpya dīpyamāno 'avatiṣṭhate|| 112.66||
etānyeva ca sarvāṇi dānāni ca tapāṃsi ca|
vinā mantreṇa satataṃ śūdrāṇām api sarvaśaḥ|| 112.67||
vidhīyate na saṃdeha evam āha prajāpatiḥ|
amantrāste smṛtāḥ sarve śūdrā vigatakalmaṣāḥ|| 112.68||
strīṇāṃ tu daivataṃ bhartā na tato 'anyadvidhīyate|
sa gatiḥ paramaṃ dhāma sa dharmaḥ paramaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 112.69||
tena yā tvabhyanujñātā imaṃ dharmaṃ samācaret|
sā phalaṃ tasya dharmasya prāpnoti susamāhitā|| 112.70||
yā tu tenānanujñātā dharmaṃ kiṃcit samācaret|
na tatphalaṃ sā labhate labhate ca satī phalam|| 112.71||
yā tu bhartrābhyanujñātā kṛtvā dharmaṃ supuṣkalam|
dadyāt tu patyuryā nārī tasyānantaṃ bhavet phalam|| 112.72||
yacca prārthayate kiṃcidiha loke paratra vā|
tat sarvaṃ prāpnute devyaḥ subhagā cāpi jāyate|| 112.73||
vaśyaścāsyā bhavedbhartā priyā tasya ca sā tadā|
putraprajā ca bhati na ca duḥkhaṃ samaśnute|| 112.74||
eṣa dharmo mayākhyāto yuṣmākaṃ lokamātaraḥ|
ato bhūyaśca kiṃ tvanyacchrotum icchatha śobhānāḥ|| 112.75||
ayaṃ hi dharmaḥ sumahānatiprabhaḥ suduskaraścāpyakṛtātmabhirvarāḥ|
na cainam anyasya śaṭhasya kasyacidadharmiṇo vā kathayīta dharmavit|| 112.76||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastāḥ sahitāḥ sarvā devyo lokasya mātaraḥ|
pūjayitvā mahādevīm ūcuḥ saṃhṛṣṭacetasaḥ|| 112.77||
aho dharmastvayākhyātaḥ sarvāmaranamaskṛte|
yasya saṃsevanāt kṣipraṃ prāpyate sumahat phalam|| 112.78||
ito vīkṣāmahe devi girerasya vanaṃ śubham|
puṣpajātisamākīrṇaṃ bahupakṣigaṇāvṛtam|| 112.79||
tata utthāya sā devī sahitā devamātṛbhiḥ|
mandarasya girerdivyaṃ draṣṭuṃ tadvanam uttamam|| 112.80||
vicacāra mahāyogā cakṣurdatvā sukhāpaham|
mānaḥśilāni śṛṅgāṇi sauvarṇāni ca vīkṣatī|| 112.81||
ramyāṇi sitatoyāni gireḥ prasravaṇāni ca|
sarāṃsyutpalapūrṇāni vāpīśca sumanoharāḥ|
tutoṣa girijā dṛṣṭvā pārśvasaṃsthaṃ ca nandinam|| 112.82||
tadā śubhāvatī nāma merukanyā sumadhyamā|
uvāca himavatputrīṃ darśayantī śubhaṃ vanam|| 112.83||
idaṃ parvatakanye tvaṃ paśya kelikalāśubham|
vanaṃ sarvartusaṃpannaṃ yathādhitvaṃ subhāṣitam|| 112.84||
ayaṃ prasūte sumahān saparvasyāsya śobhate|
viduṣām atha kṛcchreṣu yathāyuktaṃ subhāṣitam|| 112.85||
tathā svarṇopalo bhāti gireḥ śikhara uttamaḥ|
yathā lakṣaṇavadvidvān pragīya iva sāmagaḥ|| 112.86||
ayaṃ ca maṇimān nityaṃ śailāgraḥ pratibhāsvaraḥ|
bhāti udyannivāditya ubhayasto mahāyuge|| 112.87||
ayaṃ vaiduryaśikhara indranīlatalopalaḥ|
bhāti śarvāṇi vibhrāṇaḥ sthaleśvaraharopari|| 112.88||
ayaṃ matto gajo mattaḥ kareṇubhirivāvṛtaḥ|
kṛtvābhyañjanayaḥ subhru pallavaiḥ śirasā nataḥ|| 112.89||
aho surūpaṃ paśyemaṃ vanarājiyutaṃ śubhe|
yauvarājye 'abhiṣiktaṃ vai jayantam iva cāmaraiḥ|| 112.90||
pādapaṃ caiva śarvāṇi paśyainaṃ karapallavaiḥ|
mātuḥ samīpe nṛtyantaṃ putraṃ priyam ivaurasam|| 112.91||
manye priyāvāsam imaṃ devatāyā vanasya ha|
atīva dṛśyate śobhā nedṛśīṃ dṛṣṭavatyaham|| 112.92||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyāstadvacanaṃ śrutvā śubhāvatyā gireḥ sutā|
niraikṣiṣṭa taruṃ bālaṃ himavattanayāvyayā|| 112.93||
tathā sā devadevī taṃ vicarantī mahāgirau|
apaśyadbālasūryābhaṃ bālāśokaṃ supuṣpitam|| 112.94||
ātāmrapallavaśataiḥ kṛtvāñjalim avasthitam|
taṃ dṛṣṭvā girijā devī parāṃ prītim agānmune|| 112.95||
manasācintayaccaiva putro 'ayaṃ pādapo mama|
eṣa me tanayaḥ ślāghyo bhavitā nandivardhanaḥ|| 112.96||
bhagavati āgate hyenam anujñātā svayambhuvā|
grahīṣyāmi priyaṃ putraṃ bālāśokasya pādapam|| 112.97||
mama cāyam aputrāyā bhavitā pādapottamaḥ|
putraḥ putravatāṃ śreṣṭhaḥ putraśokavināśanaḥ|| 112.98||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
saivaṃ viniścitya tadā pādapaṃ prati śobhanā|
anyaṃ deśaṃ pakrimya umā tatrābhyapaśyata|| 112.99||
athāsminnantare 'abhūvannutpātāstatra bhīṣaṇāḥ|
vāyuvego mahān āsīdgirivṛkṣanipātanaḥ|| 112.100||
śikharaṃ parvatendrasya apatadvyasanaṃ vinā|
pādapāśca vinā vātam unmūlāḥ saṃbabhūvire|| 112.101||
ulkāḥ patanti cākāśādvāti vāyuraśobhanaḥ|
akṣi savyaṃ sphuraccāpi devyāstat kālinandana|| 112.102||
tān vīkṣya vismitā devī śailādim idam abravīt|
sakhīśca sarvakāleyā idaṃ vacanakovidāḥ|| 112.103||
devyuvāca|
pramatto bhāti śailo 'ayaṃ vṛkṣaistaiḥ sarvato yutaḥ|
bhayaṃ mahadidaṃ manye naitadākasmikaṃ smṛtam|| 112.104||
na cānimittam utpātā bhavantyete durāsadāḥ|
tathā kuru yathā me no bhayaṃ yacchantyaśobhanāḥ|| 112.105||
tato nandī praṇamyāha devadevīṃ kṛtāñjaliḥ|
kuto bhayaṃ bhavāni tvāṃ yā tvaṃ mātā divaukasām|| 112.106||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyaivaṃvadato vyāsa devīṃ viśvasya mātaram|
andhako 'api tadā daityaḥ pātālānmandaraṃ yayau|| 112.107||
prahlādapramukhairdaityairdānavaiśca sahasraśaḥ|
vṛtaḥ śrīmān mahādaityaḥ śakro devagaṇairiva|| 112.108||
sa daityānāṃ matenaiva variṣṭhānāṃ mahāsuraḥ|
āgato mandaraṃ draṣṭuṃ yathendro nandanaṃ vanam|| 112.109||
prahlādaścānuhlādaśca śinirbāṣkalireva ca||
huṇḍastuhuṇḍo vātāpī balirbāṇo virocanaḥ|| 112.110||
ilvalo namucirvyaṃso vipracittirmahāsuraḥ|
sundo nisundo narako dhenuko 'ariṣṭa eva ca|| 112.111||
muraḥ kārtasvanaścaiva hastī duryodhano mayaḥ|
tārakastārakākṣaśca vidyunmālī prabhākaraḥ|| 112.112||
hālāhalaśca kumbhaśca saṃvaraḥ kālasaṃvaraḥ|
dhundhustathendradamano hayagrīvaḥ śatodaraḥ|| 112.113||
meghanādaḥ siṃhanādo dundubhiḥ śatadundubhiḥ|
kālanemirbako daṇḍo vipākaḥ pāka eva ca|| 112.114||
vṛṣaparvā śatāvartaḥ pulomā śarabhastathā|
balo gaganamūrdhā ca sūcīromā mahāyaśāḥ|| 112.115||
asilomā pralambaśca śambhurdevāntakastathā|
mahiṣo bhīmasenaśca vāyurvāditra eva ca|
andhakānucarāpyete mandaraṃ samupāgatāḥ|| 112.116||
te śastravanto jitadevasaṃghā mahānubhāvā dharmapathacyutāśca|
sarve ca śūrā hyanivartinaśca sahāndhakā mandaragā babhūvuḥ|| 112.117||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tadgajānām iva kulaṃ mattānāṃ kālinandanana|
varṣatām iva meghānāṃ sviṣāṇāṃ sarīsṛpām|| 112.118||
darpitānāṃ varāhāṇāṃ mahākulam ivolbaṇam|
mandare dānavakulaṃ tathā tat pracacāra ha|| 112.119||
so 'andhako vicaraṃstatra sakhībhiḥ sahitāṃ tadā|
apaśyaddevadevī tu vṛkaḥ siṃhavadhūm iva|| 112.120||
dṛṣṭvā bhagavatīṃ devīṃ sa daityo mūḍhacetanaḥ|
praṇāmaṃ nākarodvyāsa anvavaikṣata kevalam|| 112.121||
taṃ dṛṣṭvānimiṣaṃ daityaṃ paśyantam acalātmajām|
prahlādastu mahābuddhiridam āha vaco 'arthavat|| 112.122||
iyaṃ lokasya jananī himavattanayāvyayā|
umeti jagati khyatā tapoyogabalānvitā|| 112.123||
yasya putro 'abhavadbrahmā prajāpatyaṃ ca yo dadau|
vareṇa yaśca putrasya putravatāṃ brahmaṇo gataḥ|| 112.124||
asmākaṃ devatānāṃ ca yo dadāti varāñchubhān|
āradhyaḥ sarvalokānāṃ devānāṃ ca mahāyaśāḥ|| 112.125||
yaḥ sthitaḥ sarvam āviśya bhūtagrāmam aśeṣataḥ|
yasyātmanā sarvam idaṃ dhāryate jagadavyayam|| 112.126||
yaḥ svecchayā sarvam idaṃ nimeṣārdhena saṃkṣipet|
patnīyaṃ tasya devasya parameśasya dhīmataḥ|
śaktā hīyaṃ jagat sarvaṃ kṣaṇena ditijādhipa|| 112.127||
dagdhuṃ vāpyathavā hartuṃ kṣeptuṃ naraka eva vā|
katham asyāḥ praṇāmaṃ tvaṃ nākarordaitya mohitaḥ|| 112.128||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
athaivaṃbruvatastasya dharmayuktaṃ suradviṣaḥ|
devībhiḥ sahitā devī kṣaṇonāntarhitā mune|| 112.129||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
adṛśyāḥ samapadyanta tāḥ striyo lokamātaraḥ|| 112.130||
atha te tāsu naṣṭāsu mandarasya śubhaṃ vanam|
pādacāreṇa saṃprāptā bahudṛśyasamāvṛtam|| 112.131||
balābhiḥ kalanīṣaṇḍaiḥ sātimuktapriyaṅgubhiḥ|
campakairbakulairlodhrairaśokairnāgasāhvayaiḥ|| 112.132||
puṃnāgaistilakaiścaiva devadāruvanairapi|
saralairnārikelaiśca padmaṣaṇḍaiśca śobhitam|| 112.133||
gahvaraiśca nitambaiśca guhābhirnirjharairapi|
na tasmādramaṇīyaṃ hi pṛthivyāṃ vidyate kvacit|| 112.134||
atha te daityapāḥ sarve vyacaranta mahāgirau|
bahunirjharasaṃkīrṇe nanāpādapasaṃkule|| 112.135||
tatra te vicarantastu ekasmin nirjhare sthitān|
siddhānapaśyan saptarṣīn yogayuktān mahāmunīn|| 112.136||
upaviṣṭāñchilāpaṭṭe mithaḥ kathayataḥ kathāḥ|
dharmayuktāśca citrārthā mārmikāḥ susukhāvahāḥ|| 112.137||
tān dṛṣṭvā so 'andhako 'apṛcchat prahlādam asurottamam|
ka ime ṛṣayo hyatra kimarthaṃ ceha saṃgatāḥ|| 112.138||
tam uvāca tadā dhīmānasuro devakaṇṭakam|
hiraṇyakaśipoḥ putro buddhvā madhyaṃ samāsthitaḥ|| 112.139||
prahlāda uvāca|
ete 'andhaka mahātmāna ṛṣayaḥ sapta saṃgatāḥ|
bhṛguratrirmarīciśca viśvāmitro 'aṅgirāstathā|| 112.140||
bharadvājo vasiṣṭhaśca yogasiddhāstapodhanāḥ|
ihāgatā mahātmānastapasā dagdhakilbiṣāḥ|| 112.141||
naiṣān niṣkāraṇaṃ manye mandarāgamanaṃ prabho|
ito vayam ihaikānte sthitvā sarve 'asureśvarāḥ|
jānīma kim ime kāryam iha kurvanti sādhakāḥ|| 112.142||
ete vai nibhṛtā bhūtāstūṣṇīṃ kṛtvā yathābalāḥ|
mataṃ gṛhṇīma sarveṣāṃ tūṣṇīṃ tiṣṭhata daityapāḥ|| 112.143||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste samayaṃ kṛtvā sthitā asurapuṃgavāḥ|
yo 'asmākaṃ tu vadet kiṃcidvadhyo naḥ sa bhavediti|| 112.144||
tatra teṣu sthiteṣvevam asureṣu durātmasu|
ṛṣayaste tapoyuktā vākyāni ūcuḥ parasparam|| 112.145||
na śuddho 'ayaṃ girerdeśo 'adya gacchāmo 'anyato dvijāḥ|
ihāgamo hi daityānāṃ dṛśyate sudurātmanām|| 112.146||
bhavānyapi gatānyatra asurāṇāṃ bhayārditā|
asurāste durātmāno yeṣām eṣa kṣayo dhruvaḥ|| 112.147||
gatāste nidhanaṃ sarve dharmaṃ ye nāśayannuta|
rājyārthaṃ yadi taiḥ krūrairna dharmo nāśito bhavet|| 112.148||
naivaṃ te nidhanaṃ sarve prāptāḥ syuramaradviṣaḥ|
svarājyaparisaṃtuṣṭā bhaveyuryadi saṃsthitāḥ|
te 'api sarveṣu lokeṣu babhuḥ pūjyāḥ surā iva|| 112.149||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
aṅgirāstānuvācedaṃ na teṣāṃ kāminaṃ tviha|
rājyahetoḥ pravṛttānām adharmaḥ samupasthitaḥ|| 112.150||
upārjayati rājyaṃ vai dharma eva hi kāminaḥ|
so 'adharmaṃ naiva kurvīta sthairyaṃ rājyaṃ na kiṃcana|| 112.151||
atriruvāca|
adharme rājyam icchanti jayanti yudhi sarvadā|
naḥ priyāścaiva lokasya bhavanti hitajīvinaḥ|| 112.152||
dhārmikāstvacireṇaiva hatvā śatrūnaviklavāḥ|
rājyeṣ saṃpratiṣṭhante tasmāddharmaṃ samāśrayet|| 112.153||
ye tu rājyaṃ balenaiva dharmaṃ tyaktvāśubhe ratāḥ|
icchanto 'api na tadrājyaṃ prāpnuvanti kadācana|| 112.154||
atha yat prāpyate rājyaṃ taistu krūreṇa karmaṇā|
na ciraṃ tadbhavet teṣāṃ vidviṣṭāśca bhavantyuta|| 112.155||
bhṛguruvāca|
dharma eṣa purā prāpto hyasurāṇāṃ bhayāvahaḥ|
brahmaṇā sṛṣṭikāmena na ca te vartayantyuta|| 112.156||
svabhāvena ca te sarve dāruṇā vai nisargataḥ|
dāruṇābhigamāccaiva tat karma samupāśritāḥ|| 112.157||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
asurān prati teṣāṃ tu evaṃkathayatāṃ tadā|
āgāddhātā vidhātā ca kṛtāntaśceti te trayaḥ|| 112.158||
tāṃste saṃpūjya vidhivat parasparam anuvratāḥ|
upaviṣṭāḥ śilāsveva munuyo 'api ca te trayaḥ|| 112.159||
upaviṣṭāṃścarṣayastānanamaṃśca bahumānataḥ|
ūcuḥ kvedaṃ bhavanto 'adya prasthitā lokadhāriṇaḥ|| 112.160||
dhātovāca|
brahmalokāddhyupāvṛtya vayam adya gatā dvijāḥ|
brahmaṇā sma samājñaptāḥ kaśyapasya tato 'antikam|| 112.161||
bhūyo 'api munayaḥ procurvimuktaḥ kaśyapo dvijaḥ|
athābravīnmunīn dhātā kaśyapaṃ tu yaduktavān|| 112.162||
yat tvayā jñāpito brahman brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
asurā api me putrā devāścāpi priyāḥ prabho|| 112.163||
teṣāṃ naiva yathānyonyaṃ vairaṃ syāllokabhāvana|
tathā kurvamaraśreṣṭha bhaveyaṃ nirvṛtastataḥ|| 112.164||
tatrāhaṃ brahmaṇājñapto bravīmi tvāṃ mahāmune|
devāsuraṃ yathāvṛttam anyonyaṃ sakhyam eva ca|| 112.165||
amṛtotpādanaṃ caiva rājyaṃ saṃsthāṃ ca kṛtsnaśaḥ|
tvayoktaṃ bhagavān sarvaṃ bhaviṣyam ṛṣisattama|| 112.166||
kathayāmāsa lokeśo devāsuraviceṣṭitam|
nivedya tasya tat sarvaṃ brahmaṇā preṣitā vayam|
ihāgatā bhagavatīṃ draṣṭuṃ himagireḥ sutām|| 112.167||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tānevaṃvādino bhūya ṛṣayaste tapodhanāḥ|
papracchurniyatātmānaḥ sarva eva tadā mune|| 112.168||
devāsurāṇāṃ yadvṛttaṃ bhaviṣyaṃ kathitaṃ śubhāḥ|
tadvayaṃ śrotum icchāmo yadi vo 'anugrahe matiḥ|| 112.169||
kiṃ ca vijñāpitā devī yuṣmābhiḥ surasattamāḥ|
kathayadhvaṃ ca tat sarvaṃ yadyanugrāhyatā hi naḥ|| 112.170||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā trayaste devasattamāḥ|
tvam ācakṣva kṛtānteti vākyam ūcurmahābalāḥ|| 112.171||
tataḥ sa teṣāṃ bahucitrakāraṇaṃ yathā bhaviṣyaṃ kathayāṃ cakāra|
surāsurāṇāṃ jagataśca kāraṇaṃ purā vidhātrā vihitaṃ yathārthavat|| 112.172||
iti skandapurāṇe mandarārohaṇo nāma dvādaśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 112.112||

skandapurana113
vyāsa uvāca|
yat teṣāṃ kathitaṃ tena kṛtāntena mahātmanā|
ṛṣīṇāṃ mandare pūrvaṃ tat sarvaṃ kathayasva me|| 113.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
bhaviṣyatyasurāṇāṃ tu hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ|
indro mahābalo vidvān prahlādo 'asurapuṃgavaḥ|| 113.2||
so 'amṛtaṃ saha devaistu kṛtvā suragaṇādhipaḥ|
jitvā yuddhe 'amṛtaṃ devān nītavān daityapuṃgavaḥ|
viṣṇunā nirjito yuddhe putraṃ rājye 'abhiṣekṣyati|| 113.3||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ tadamṛtaṃ devairasuraiśca mahābalaiḥ|
mathitaṃ brahmaṇaḥ putra etadicchāmi veditum|| 113.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
brahmaṇābhyetya śakratve prahlādo 'asurapuṃgavaḥ|
abhiṣiktastadā vyāsa asurān prajugopa ha|| 113.5||
atha devaistadā saṃkhyam asurāṇāṃ babhūva ha|
amantrayanta devāśca bhagavantaṃ pitāmaham|| 113.6||
devā ūcuḥ|
bhagavannasurairdevā hanyante yudhi martyavat|
na mriyante yathā devāstathājñāpaya suvrata|| 113.7||
sa evam uktastān āha brahmā devān savāsavān|
kṣīrodādamṛtaṃ śīghram utpādayata gacchata|| 113.8||
manvantareṣu sarveṣu ye ye devā bhavanti te|
kṣīrodādamṛtaṃ sarve janayantyasuraiḥ saha|| 113.9||
tadaśnanti ca deveśāstena tṛptiśca jāyate|
uttiṣṭhanti mṛtāścaiva pītvā ca na mriyanti te|| 113.10||
devā ūcuḥ|
kathaṃ tadamṛtaṃ devā bhuvi manvantareśvarāḥ|
utpādayanti tat sarvam upāyaṃ kathayasva naḥ|| 113.11||
brahmovāca|
vāruṇyāṃ somapuryāṃ tu kṣīrodaṃ tat saraḥ śubham|
samudrā yatra te sapta sadā saṃnihitāḥ śubhāḥ|| 113.12||
irā mālā sinīvālī kuhū rākā irāvatī|
sāvitrī caiva gāyatrī surabhī kadrureva ca|| 113.13||
aditiśca ditiścaiva devikā viśvasaṃbhavā|
gāvaḥ sarvasahā yatra sarvakāmadughāḥ śubhāḥ|| 113.14||
kṣaranti vatsalāḥ kṣīraṃ ṣaḍrasaṃ hyamṛtopamam|
ṛṣayaḥ phenapā yatra tapodamaśamātmakāḥ|| 113.15||
oṣadhyastatra yāḥ kāścilloke 'asmin devasattamāḥ|
grāmyāraṇyāśca divyāśca mānuṣāśca sahasraśaḥ|| 113.16||
vṛkṣān vallirvīrudhaśca gulmānanyāṃśca tādṛśān|
prakṣipya bheṣajaṃ caiva somaṃ rājānam eva ca|| 113.17||
śriyaṃ lakṣmīṃ tathā khyātiṃ yaśastuṣṭiṃ tathaiva ca|
kīrtiṃ śraddhāṃ dhāraṇāṃ ca ūhāpohe tathaiva ca|| 113.18||
balaṃ dharmam athorjaśca tṛptiṃ devīṃ sarasvatīm|
tīrthāni caiva sarvāṇi dānāni vividhāni ca|| 113.19||
vṛṣaṃ rathaṃ dhvajaṃ caiva gajam aśvaṃ tathaiva ca|
aṣṭau ca maṅgalānyatra tathā chandāṃsi cākṣipan|| 113.20||
vedān vidyāśca yāḥ kāścidyāścaitā lokamātaraḥ|
mantrānyajñān suvarṇaṃ ca mantropakaraṇāni ca|| 113.21||
yat kiṃcicchobhanaṃ caiva tṛptimadrasavacca ha|
prakṣipya tatra tat sarvaṃ tato manthānam āvahan|| 113.22||
mandaraṃ parvataśreṣṭham akūpāraṃ ca kacchapam|
tasya pṛṣṭhe ca manthānaṃ mandaraṃ parvateśvaram|| 113.23||
kṛtvā viṣṇugṛhītaṃ te vāsukiṃ pragrahaṃ tathā|
yato mukhaṃ tato daityā yataḥ pucchaṃ tataḥ surāḥ|| 113.24||
karṣantastaṃ tu manthānaṃ mathnanti bahulāḥ samāḥ|
tato varṣasahasreṇa tasmādutthāsyate hayaḥ|| 113.25||
gāvaścaiva sahābhāgā gajo mattaśca vai śubhaḥ|
vṛṣabho bhīmanādaśca kanyāḥ kīcakaveṇavaḥ|| 113.26||
aṣṭamaṅgalakaṃ caiva bhiṣagdhanvantaristathā|
śrīrlakṣmīrevamādyāśca vāruṇī ca madotkaṭā|| 113.27||
oṣadhyaśca tathā divyā grāmyāraṇyāḥ samānuṣāḥ|
vṛkṣādayaśca te sarve tataḥ somaśca pārthivaḥ|| 113.28||
amṛtaṃ tat samāhṛtya viṣaṃ tacca durāsadam|
yajñādīṃścaiva tat sarvān yat kiṃcit tatra saṃbhṛtam|| 113.29||
evaṃ manvantareṣvatra devaiḥ sāsuramānuṣaiḥ|
mathyate tvamṛtaṃ devāstacca saṃjāyate tathā|| 113.30||
tasmādyūyam ito gatvā dānavaiḥ saha devatāḥ|
manthadhvam amṛtaṃ kṣipraṃ tataḥ prāpsyatha taddhitam|| 113.31||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā deveśā brahmaṇā lokakartṛṇā|
imaṃ lokam upāvṛtya tathā kurvanta sarvaśaḥ|| 113.32||
tasmiṃstu mathyamāne vai viṣam agre samutthitam|
devāsuratrāsakaraṃ tat papau śaṃkarastadā|| 113.33||
tatastasmāt punarapi hyudatiṣṭhan payonidheḥ|
ratnāni bahucitrāṇi tānyagṛhṇanta devatāḥ|| 113.34||
asurā jagṛhurnaitānyaśapaṃstāṃstato 'asurān|
maṅgalānyavamanyanta tena te nidhanaṃ gatāḥ|| 113.35||
ratnāni ūcuḥ|
yasmādyūyaṃ durātmāno nāsmān nandatha dāruṇāḥ|
tasmāt samīhitaṃ yadvastat tathā na bhaviṣyati|| 113.36||
vāruṇīṃ nāpyagṛhṇantāsurā madabalāvahām|
yasmāt tato 'asurāste vai durātmānaśca sarvaśaḥ|| 113.37||
tata uccaiḥśravā nāma vājī paramaśobhanaḥ|
hastī caiva caturdanto bhiṣak ca sumahāyaśāḥ|| 113.38||
ghṛtācī pūrvacittiśca devī rambhā manoramā|
amṛtaṃ ca tataḥ somo gṛhītvotthitavān surāḥ|| 113.39||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tata utsṛjya te ratnānyasurā darpitā bhṛśam|
somahastādbalenaiva amṛtaṃ jagṛhustadā|| 113.40||
tān devāḥ sahitābhyetya ūcuḥ sāntvena mohitān|
na yuktaṃ kartum evaṃ vaḥ sahitā upayuñjmahe|| 113.41||
sakhyaṃ hi no 'astu sudṛḍhaṃ mā no balamadānvitāḥ|
kleśam enaṃ vṛthā yeha kurudhvaṃ dānaveśvarāḥ|| 113.42||
tāṃstathāvādinaḥ sarvān prahlādo dānaveśvaraḥ|
idam āha mahāmāyo dharmaṃ kṛtvā tu pṛṣṭhataḥ|| 113.43||
prahlāda uvāca|
yadā ratnānyagṛhṇīdhvaṃ sāgarādutthitāni vai|
tadā na yūyam asmābhiḥ kiṃciduktāḥ sureśvarāḥ|| 113.44||
idam evaṃ vayaṃ sarve ratnaṃ gṛhṇīma devatāḥ|
naitadvinā hi yuddhena dāsyāmo vayam adya vai|| 113.45||
idam asmadgataṃ devā amṛtaṃ sarvamaṅgalam|
yuddhena yadi vaḥ kāryaṃ gṛhṇīdhvaṃ yadi śakyate|| 113.46||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evamuktāstaiḥ krūrairdevā bhītā ivābhavan|
vivarṇavadanā dīnā na kiṃcit tāṃstadocire|| 113.47||
vrīḍitāste mahāsattvā vinivṛttāḥ sureśvarāḥ|
nirutsāhā babhūvurhi hatā smeti ca cintayan|| 113.48||
tāṃstathā cintayānāṃstu sahasrākṣaḥ puraṃdaraḥ|
uvāca kiṃ viṣādena yuddhenainān nihanmahe|| 113.49||
viṣṇuruvāca|
abuddhireṣa śakrasya yuddhaṃ prati sureśvarāḥ|
na hi yuddhe 'asurāḥ śakyāḥ sarve hantuṃ mahābalāḥ|| 113.50||
tasmāt te na pibanti sma yāvadevāmṛtaṃ śubham|
tāvadeva hariṣyāmi māyām āsthāya tacchalāt|| 113.51||
saṃnahyadhvaṃ surāḥ sarve vyūhaṃ kṛtvāvatiṣṭhata|
gṛhītvā yāvadamṛtam ihāyāmi divaukasaḥ|| 113.52||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ saṃmohinīṃ māyām āsthāya vibudheśvarāḥ|
yajñaśrīrasmi saṃprāptā dānavān baladarpitān|| 113.55||
pratigṛhṇantu māṃ sarve dānavāḥ suravidviṣaḥ|
gatāste nidhanaṃ devā yūyaṃ devā na saṃśayaḥ|| 113.56||
tato 'asurāstadotthāya prahlādaścaiva dānavaḥ|
pradakṣiṇam upāvṛtya haste 'asya kalaśaṃ daduḥ|| 113.57||
sa prāha dānavān devaḥ strīrūpākṛṣṭamānasān|
nedaṃ mayi bhavanto 'adya kṣeptum arhanti sarvaśaḥ|| 113.58||
māyām āsthāya vibudhā māhārṣaste kadācana|
te hi sarve durācārā māyānikṛtam āśritāḥ|| 113.59||
prahlāda uvāca|
jāne māyāvidaste vai nikṛtyā balinaśca ha|
māyayaiva vayaṃ tān vai nihaṃsyāmaḥ sudaṃśitān|| 113.60||
nikṛtyā nikṛtijñāstu hantavyā duṣṭacetasaḥ|
māyāvidaśca māyābhiriti dharma prabhāṣitam|| 113.61||
tvaṃ tu no gatiradyeha tathā caiva parāyaṇam|
tvayā dattam idaṃ sarve upoyakṣyāma śobhane|| 113.62||
tvaṃ cenna yacchase 'asmākaṃ taddhi te paramaṃ hitam|
vayaṃ ca tvāṃ tathā sarve nāvamaṃsyāmahe sadā|| 113.63||
tataḥ sa taṃ tadā dhīmān prahasya śubhadarśanaḥ|
uvāca yat tvayā gītaṃ satyaṃ tacca karomi te|| 113.64||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato nirīkṣatāṃ teṣāṃ viṣṇuḥ kṛtvā svakaṃ vapuḥ|
pragṛhyāmṛtam utpatya devebhyaḥ pradadau vibhuḥ|| 113.65||
iti skandapurāṇe amṛtāharaṇe trayodaśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 113.113||

skandapurana114
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ tadutthitaṃ ghoraṃ viṣaṃ sūryāyutaprabham|
kathaṃ pītaṃ bhagavatā śaṃkareṇāmitaujasā|| 114.1||
kathaṃ ca devadevasya kaṇṭhe kundendusaprabhe|
nīlo varṇaḥ samutpanna etadicchāmi veditum|| 114.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
kasmin deśe mahāpuṇye etadākhyānam uttamam|
vṛttaṃ brahmapurogāya kasmin kāle mahādyute|| 114.3||
etadākhyāhi naḥ samyagyathāvṛttaṃ tapodhana|
nīlakaṇṭhaḥ kathaṃ devaḥ śarvastribhuvaneśvaraḥ|| 114.4||
sūta uvāca|
yathā śrutaṃ mayā pūrvaṃ vāyunā jagadāyunā|
kathyamānaṃ dvijaśreṣṭhāḥ sattre varṣasahasrike|| 114.5||
nīlatā kena kaṇṭhasya devadevasya śūlinaḥ|
tadahaṃ kīrtayiṣyāmi śṛṇudhvaṃ saṃśritavratāḥ|| 114.6||
uttare śailarājasya sarāṃsi sarito hradāḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- kīrṇeṣu deśeṣu parvateṣu ca|| 114.7||
giriśṛṅgeṣu tuṅgeṣu gahvaropavaneṣu ca|
-- bhakṣā mahātmāno munayaḥ śaṃsitavratāḥ|| 114.8||
saṃstuvanti mahādevaṃ yajanto 'atra yathāvidhi|
ṛgyajuḥsāmavedaiśca nṛtyagītārcanādibhiḥ|| 114.9||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
pravṛtte jyotiṣāṃ cakre madhyaṃ prāpte divākare|| 114.10||
daivatā niyatātmānaḥ sarve tiṣṭhanti tāṃ kalām|
niyamāni samāpyānte tasmin kāle divaukasām|| 114.11||
teṣāṃ madhye gato vāyuḥ prāṇināṃ jīvitodbhavaḥ|
namaste nīlakaṇṭhāya ityuvāca sadāgatiḥ|| 114.12||
tacchrutvā bhāvitātmāno munayaḥ saṃśitavratāḥ|
bālakhilyā iti khyātāḥ pataṅgasahacāriṇaḥ|| 114.13||
aṣṭāśītisahasrāṇi munīnām ūrdhvaretasām|
te sma pṛcchanti vai vāyuṃ vāyuparṇāmbubhojanāḥ|| 114.14||
bālakhilyā ūcuḥ|
nīlakaṇṭheti yat proktaṃ tvayā pavanasattama|
tadvayaṃ śrotum icchāma tvatprasādāt prabhañjana|| 114.15||
nīlatā kena kaṇṭhasya prakāreṇāmbikāpateḥ|
śrotum icchāmahe samyak tvadvaktrāt tu viśeṣataḥ|| 114.16||
etat pṛṣṭaṃ yadasmābhistaddhi naḥ paramaṃ hitam|
vāco yāḥ saṃpravartante sarvāstāstu tvayeritāḥ|| 114.17||
varṇasthānagate vāyau vāgvidhiḥ saṃpravartate|
jñānaṃ vijñānam utsāhastvatto vāyo pravartate|| 114.18||
-- -- -- -- -- o i o na yogena sarve varṇāḥ pravartitāḥ|
yato vāco nivartante dehabaddhāśca durlabhāḥ|| 114.19||
tatrāpi te 'asti sadbhāvaḥ sarvagastvaṃ sadānila|
nānyaḥ sarvagato devastvadṛte 'asti samīraṇa|| 114.20||
sa caiva jīvaloko 'ayaṃ dhāritaḥ pavana tvayā|
eṣa vai jīvalokaste pratyakṣo jīvitodbhava|| 114.21||
vettha vācaspatiṃ devaṃ manonāyakam īśvaram|
brūhi tvaṃ kena deśe 'asya kiṃ kṛtā rūpavikriyā|| 114.22||
śrutvā vākyaṃ tatasteṣām ṛṣīṇāṃ bhāvitāmanām|
pratyuvāca mahātejā vāyurlokanamaskṛtaḥ|| 114.23||
vāyuruvāca|
purā kṛtayuge viprā vedanirṇayatatparaḥ|
vasiṣṭho nāma dharmātmā mānaso vai prajāpatiḥ|| 114.24||
papraccha kārttikeyaṃ vai mayūravaravāhanam|
krauñcadehāntakaraṇaṃ devyā hṛdayanandanam|| 114.25||
mahiṣāsuranārīṇāṃ nayanāñjanataskaram|
mahāsenaṃ mahātmānaṃ bālakaṃ chadmarūpiṇam|| 114.26||
bahumaṅgalasaṃyuktāṃ kathāṃ pāpapraṇāśanīm|
vasiṣṭhaḥ prārthayāmāsa tasmin kāle mahātapāḥ|| 114.27||
vasiṣṭha uvāca|
śuciṃ prapadye varadaṃ brahmaṇyam amitaujasam|
bhaktānukampinaṃ nityaṃ sarvajñaṃ priyadarśanam|| 114.28||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- m|
namaste -- -- -- ṣyanda agnigarbha namo 'astu te|| 114.29||
namaste śarajanmāya namaste kṛttikāsuta|
namo dvādaśanetrāya ṣaṇmukhāya namo 'astu te|| 114.30||
namaste śaktihastāya divyasra -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- || 114.31||
namo hiraṇyaretāya namaste bhṛtaśambhave|
namaḥ kukkuṭahastāya tathā chāgapriyāya ca|| 114.32||
namaste raktavāsāya namo nīlaśikhaṇḍine|
namo 'atyantakumārāya sarvadaivatapūjite|| 114.33||
namaḥ krauñcavināśāya mahiṣāsuraghātine|
namaste 'arṇava -- -- -- mūrtaye -- -- -- -- --|| 114.34||
namaste bālarūpāya unmattalalitāya ca|
yadetaddṛśyate sthāṇoḥ śubhaṃ śubhrāñjanopamam|| 114.35||
tat kimarthaṃ samutpannaṃ kaṇṭhe kundendusaṃnibhe|
etadāptāya dāntāya bhaktāya tava pṛcchate|| 114.36||
brūhi maṅgalasaṃyuktāṃ kathāṃ puṇyasamāśritām|
evaṃstuto vasiṣṭhena muninā bhāvitātmanā|| 114.37||
śrutvā vākyaṃ tatastasya vasiṣṭhasya mahātmanaḥ|
pratyuvāca mahātejā daityāriḥ pāvakodbhavaḥ|| 114.38||
yaduktaṃ bhavatā praśnaṃ yanmāṃ pṛcchasi vai dvija|
śrūyatāṃ vadatāṃ śreṣṭha kathyamānam idam mayā|| 114.39||
umotsaṅgopaviṣṭena yathā pūrvaṃ mayā śrutaḥ|
pārvatyāścaiva saṃvādaḥ śaṃkarasya mahātmanaḥ|| 114.40||
tam ahaṃ saṃpravakṣyāmi yathātathyaṃ mahāmune|
kailāsaśikhare ramye nānādhātuvicitrite|| 114.41||
taruṇādityasaṃkāśe taptakāñcanasaṃnibhe|
vajrasphaṭikasopāne citrapaṭṭaśilātale|| 114.42||
jāmbūnadamaye divye nānāratnavibhūṣite|
nānādrumalatākīrṇe nānāpuṣpaphalodake|| 114.43||
haṃsakāraṇḍavākīrṇe cakravākopaśobhite|
ṣaṭpadodgītakamale dhārāsampātanādite|| 114.44||
mattakrauñcamayūrāṇāṃ nādairvikruṣṭakandare|
apsarogaṇasaṃkīrṇe kiṃnaraiścopaśobhite|| 114.45||
jīvaṃjīvakadātyūhavirutaiśca praṇādite|
kokilārāvamadhure siddhacāraṇasevite|| 114.46||
saurabheyaninādāḍhye meghastanitanisvane|
vināyakabhayodvignaiḥ kuñjarairmuktakandare|| 114.47||
vaṃśavāditranirghoṣe śrotrendriyamanohare|
dolālalitavikṣepairvanitāsiddhasevite|| 114.48||
dhvajairlambitadolānāṃ ghaṇṭānāṃ virutākule|
ballakīghoṣabahule nṛttavyāpārasaṃkule|| 114.49||
mukhairdaṛdaravādyaiśca valgitāsphoṭite tathā|
krīḍāceṣṭāvinodānāṃ ravairākrandakandare|| 114.50||
hāsaiḥ saṃtrāsajananairvikarālaistathā mukhaiḥ|
dehabandhairvicitraiśca prakrīḍitagaṇeśvare|| 114.51||
vyāghrasiṃhamukhairghoraiḥ sarpākhuvadanairapi|
mṛgameṣamukhaiścānyairgajavājimukhaistathā|| 114.52||
viḍālavadanaiścograiḥ kroṣṭukākāramūrtibhiḥ|
hrasvairdīrghaiḥ kṛśaiḥ sthūlairlambodaramahodaraiḥ|| 114.53||
hrasvajaṅghaiḥ pralamboṣṭhaistālajaṅghaistathāparaiḥ|
gokarṇairekakarṇaiśca mahākarṇairakarṇakaiḥ|| 114.54||
ekapādairmahāpādairbahupādairapādakaiḥ|
ekamūrdhabhiratyugrairbahumūrdhabhirulbaṇaiḥ|| 114.55||
amūrdhabhiśca gaṇapairmahāmūrdhabhireva ca|
ekanetrairmahānetrairbahunetraiśca sarvaśaḥ|| 114.56||
kabandhākṛtibhiścānyairanetrairgaṇanāyakaiḥ|
ekanāsairmahānāsairbahunāsairanāsikaiḥ|| 114.57||
ekavaktairmahāvaktrairbahuvaktrairavaktrakaiḥ|
ekadaṃṣṭrairmahādaṃṣṭrairbahudaṃṣṭrairadaṃṣṭrakaiḥ|| 114.58||
ekahastairmahāhastairbahuhastairahastakaiḥ|
viśvarūpairvirūpaiśca surūpai rūpavarjitaiḥ|
evaṃvidhairmahāyogairbhūtairbhūtapatirvṛtaḥ|| 114.59||
viśuddharatnāṅgavibhūṣitāṅgadā śilātale hemamaye manorame|
sukhopaviṣṭaṃ madanāṅganāśanaṃ cucoda vākyaṃ girirājyanandanā|| 114.60||
devyuvāca|
bhagavan bhūtabhavyeśa govṛṣāṅkita śāsana|
tava kaṇṭhe mahādeva bhrājate 'ambudasaṃnibham|| 114.61||
nātyulbaṇaṃ śubhaṃ śubhraṃ nīlāñjanacayopamam|
kim idaṃ deva dīptaṃ te kaṇṭhe kāmāṅganāśana|
ko hetuḥ kāraṇaṃ kiṃ vā yenedaṃ nīlam īśvara|
etat sarvaṃ yathānyāyaṃ śrotum icchāmi tattvataḥ|| 114.62||
śrutvā vākyaṃ tato devyāḥ pārvatyāḥ pārvatīpriyaḥ|
kathāṃ maṅgalasaṃyuktāṃ kathayāmāsa śaṃkaraḥ|| 114.63||
maheśvara uvāca|
mathyamāne 'amṛte pūrvaṃ kṣīrode suradānavaiḥ|
agre samutthitaṃ ghoraṃ viṣaṃ kālānalaprabham|| 114.64||
kālamṛtyurivodbhūtaṃ yugāntādityavarcasam|
trailokyotsādasūryābhaṃ visphurat tat samantataḥ|| 114.65||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā surasaṃghāśca daityāścaiva varānane|
viṣaṇṇavadanāḥ sarve gatāste brahmaṇo 'antikam|| 114.66||
dṛṣṭvā suragaṇān bhītān brahmovāca mahādyutiḥ|
mayāṣṭaguṇam aiśvaryaṃ bhavatāṃ saṃprakalpitam|| 114.67||
trailokyasyeśvarā yūyaṃ sarve ca vigatajvarāḥ|
vimānacāriṇaḥ sarve sarve svacchandacāriṇaḥ|| 114.68||
prajābhiḥ satkṛtāḥ samyaṅnityaṃ bahumatā mama|
kimarthe vā mahāprajñā bhṛśam udvignacetasaḥ|| 114.69||
kena vyāvartitaiśvaryā yena māṃ samupasthitāḥ|
prajāsarge na so 'atrāsti yo 'ajñānmama nivartayet|| 114.70||
adhyātme cādhibhūte ca adhidaive ca nityaśaḥ|
prajākarmavipāke ca śaktā yūyaṃ pravartitum|| 114.71||
kiṃ kāryaṃ kāraṇaṃ kiṃ vā kuto vā bhayam āgatam|
yena yūyaṃ samudvignā mṛgāḥ siṃhārditā iva|| 114.72||
etat sarvaṃ yathānyāyaṃ śīghram ākhyātum arhatha|
śrutvā vākyaṃ tatastasya brahmaṇaḥ sumahātmanaḥ|| 114.73||
ūcusta ṛṣibhiḥ sārdhaṃ suradaityendradānavāḥ|
surāsuragaṇairbrahman mathyamāne mahodadhau|| 114.74||
bhujaṃgabhṛṅgasaṃkāśaṃ nīlajīmūtasaṃnibham|
prādurbhūtaṃ viṣaṃ ghoraṃ saṃvarttāgnisamaprabham|| 114.75||
kālamṛtyurivodbhūtaṃ yugāntāgnisamaprabham|
trailokyotsādasūryābhaṃ visphurat tat samantataḥ|| 114.76||
tejasām iva saṃghātaṃ sumahat samupasthitam|
viṣaṇṇavadanāḥ sarve dṛṣṭodbhūtaṃ mahāviṣam|| 114.77||
viṣenottiṣṭhatā tena kālānalasamatviṣā|
nirdagdho raktagaurāṅgaḥ kṛtaḥ kṛṣṇo janārdanaḥ|| 114.78||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā raktagaurāṅgaṃ kṛtaṃ kṛṣṇaṃ janārdanam|
sarve bhītā vayaṃ brahmaṃstvām eva śaraṇaṃ gatāḥ|| 114.79||
surāṇām asurāṇāṃ ca śrutvā vākyaṃ bhayāvaham|
pratyuvāca mahātejā brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|| 114.80||
śṛṇvantu devatāḥ sarve ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
yat tadagre samudbhūtaṃ mathyamāne mahodadhau|| 114.81||
viṣaṃ kālānalaprakhyaṃ kālakūṭam iti śrutam|
tasya prodbhūtamātrasya virājante na devatāḥ|| 114.82||
tasya viṣṇurahaṃ vāpi sarve vā surapuṃgavāḥ|
śaknuvanti na vai soḍhuṃ vegam anyatra śaṃkarāt|| 114.83||
ityuktvā padmagarbhābhaḥ padmayonirayonijaḥ|
mām evaṃ stotum ārebhe brahmā vedavidāṃ varaḥ|| 114.84||
brahmovāca|
namastubhyaṃ virūpākṣa namaste naikacakṣuṣe|
namaḥ pinākahastāya vajrahastāya vai namaḥ|| 114.85||
namastriśūlahastāya daṇḍapāśāsipāṇaye|
namastrailokyanāthāya bhūtānāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 114.86||
namaḥ surārihantre ca somasūryāgnicakṣuṣe|
brahmaṇe caiva rudrāya viṣṇave caiva te namaḥ|| 114.87||
sāṃkhyāya caiva yogāya bhūtagrāmāya vai namaḥ|
manmathāṅgavināśāya kālakālāya vai namaḥ|| 114.88||
rudrāya vasuretāya devadevāya raṃhase|
uṣṇīṣiṇe suvaktrāya sahasrākṣāya mīḍhuṣe|| 114.89||
kapardine karālāya śaṃkarāya harāya ca|
virūpāya surūpāya śivāya varadāya ca|| 114.90||
tripuraghne makhaghnāyamātR̥ṇāṃ pataye namaḥ|
buddhāya caiva śuddhāya muktāya kevalāya ca|| 114.91||
lokatrayavidhātre ca śakrāya varadāya ca|
ugrāyātha tathogrāya viprāyānantacakṣuṣe|| 114.92||
rajase caiva sattvāya tamase 'avyaktayonaye|
nityāya caivānityāya nityānityāya vai namaḥ|| 114.93||
vyaktāya caivāvyaktāya vyaktāvyaktāya vai namaḥ|
cintyāya caivācintyāya cintyācintyāya vai namaḥ|| 114.94||
sūkṣmāya caivāsūkṣmāya sūkṃsāsūkṣmāya vai namaḥ|
bhaktānām ārtināśāya priyanarāyaṇāya ca|| 114.95||
umāpriyāya śarvāya nandivaktrāṅkanāya ca|
pakṣamāsārdhamāsāya ṛtusaṃvatsarāya ca|| 114.96||
bahurūpāya muṇḍāya daṇḍine 'atha varūthine|
rathine dhanvine nityaṃ jaṭine brahmacāriṇe|| 114.97||
ṛgyajuḥsāmarūpāya puruṣāyeśvarāya ca|
namaste bhagavan tryakṣa namaste bhagavañchiva|| 114.98||
namaste devadeveśa namaste bhūtabhāvana|
ityevamādicaritaiḥ stutaṃ stutyaṃ namo 'astu te|| 114.99||
praṇamya mūrdhnā praṇato 'asmi rudraṃ jagadguruṃ devavaraṃ trinetram|
sūkṣmo 'asi yogātiśayādhigamyaṃ tejonidhe vyaktam upaisi rudram|| 114.100||
jñātvā tu bhaktiṃ mama devadeva prasīda gaṅgāmbuniṣiktakeśa|
tvāṃ saurabheyāmbudacitrayānaṃ śivaṃ prayatnāt śaraṇaṃ gato 'asmi|| 114.101||
evaṃ tena tadā pūrvaṃ brahmaṇā lokakartṛṇā|
stuto 'ahaṃ vividhaiḥ stotrairvedavedāṅgasambhavaiḥ|| 114.102||
tataḥ prīto hyahaṃ tasya brahmaṇo 'atha mahātmanaḥ|
namastaṃ mukhyayā vṛttyā pitāmaham athābruvam|| 114.103||
bhagavan bhūtabhavyeśa bhūtādhipa mahātapaḥ|
kiṃ kāryaṃ te mayā brahman kartavyaṃ vada suvrata|
śrutvā vākyaṃ tato brahmā pratyuvācāmbujekṣaṇe|| 114.104||
brahmovāca|
bhūtabhavyabhavannātha śrūyatāṃ kāraṇeśvara|
surāsuragaṇairdeva mathyamāne mahodadhau|| 114.105||
mayūrabhṛṅgasaṃkāśaṃ nīlajīmūtasaṃnibham|
prādurbhūtaṃ viṣaṃ ghoraṃ saṃvarttāgnisamaprabham|| 114.106||
kālamṛtyurivodbhūtaṃ yugāntādityavarcasam|
trailokyotsādasūryābhaṃ visphurat tat samantataḥ|| 114.107||
viṣeṇottiṣṭhatā tena kālānalasamatviṣā|
nirdagdho raktagaurāṅgaḥ kṛtaḥ kṛṣṇo janārdanaḥ|| 114.108||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā raktagaurāṅgaṃ kṛtaṃ kṛṣṇaṃ janārdanam|
tataḥ sarve vayaṃ bhītāstvām eva śaraṇaṃ gatāḥ|| 114.109||
tat pibasva mahādeva lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā|
bhavānagrasya bhoktā vai bhavān devavaraḥ prabhuḥ|| 114.110||
bhavāṃstasya mahāvegaṃ samarthaḥ saṃniyacchitum|
nānyaḥ kaścit pumāñchakto jagatyasmiṃścarācare|| 114.111||
pātum eko mahādeva samarthastvaṃ mahādyute|
tasyaivograprabhāvasya kālānalasamatviṣaḥ|| 114.112||
vegaṃ soḍhuṃ mahādeva samartho 'anyo na vidyate|
tasyaivaṃ bruvato devi brahmaṇaḥ parameṣṭhinaḥ|| 114.113||
bāḍham ityeva tadvākyaṃ pratigṛhya varānane|
tadahaṃ pātum ārabdho viṣam antakasaṃnibham|| 114.114||
lokatrayahitārthāya suradaityendrasaṃnidhau|
pibato me mahāghoraṃ viṣaṃ surag.anārcite|
kaṇṭhe samabhavat kṣipraṃ kṛṣṇaṃ kṛṣṇābuje kṣaṇe|| 114.115||
taddṛṣṭvotpalapatrābhaṃ kaṇṭhe saktaṃ mahāviṣam|
takṣakaṃ nāgarājānaṃ lelihānam ivoragam|| 114.116||
athovāca mahātejā brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
śobhase tvaṃ mahādeva kaṇṭhenānena suvrata|| 114.117||
iti tasya vacaḥ śrutvā mayā girivarātmaje|
paśyatāṃ surasaṃghānāṃ daityānāṃ ca varānane|| 114.118||
yakṣagandharvasiddhānāṃ piśācoragarakṣasām|
dhṛtaṃ kaṇṭhe viṣaṃ ghoraṃ tataḥ śrīkaṇṭhatā mama|| 114.119||
tat kālakūṭaṃ viṣam ugratejaḥ kaṇṭhe dhṛtaṃ parvatarājakanye|
paśyan samastaḥ suradaityasaṃgho hṛṣṭaḥ paraṃ vismayam ājagāma|| 114.120||
tataḥ suragaṇāḥ sarve sayakṣoragarākṣasāḥ|
ūcuḥ prāñjalayo devi mattamātaṅgagāmini|| 114.121||
aho balaṃ vīryaparākramaste aho vapuryogabalaṃ tavedam|
aho vibhūtistava devadeva gaṅgājalaplāvitacandramaule|| 114.122||
tvam eva viṣṇuścaturānanastvaṃ tvam eva sūryo rajanīkarastvam|
tvam eva kālo niyatistvam eva tvam eva mṛtyurdhanadastvam eva|| 114.123||
tvam eva sūkṣmaḥ puruṣo 'avyayastvaṃ tvam eva sūkṣmācca paraṃ ca sūkṣmam|
vyaktaṃ tvam eva prakṛtistvam eva tvam eva sattvaṃ ca bhavodbhavaṃ ca|| 114.124||
tvam eva bhūmiḥ salilaṃ tvam eva tvam eva vahniḥ pavanastvam eva|
tvam eva khaṃ bhūtabhaviṣyabhavyaṃ tvam eva bhūtaṃ bhavabhavyayuktam|| 114.125||
tvam eva yajño niyamastvam eva tvam eva sarvaṃ prakaroṣi dharmam|
tvam eva sarvasya carācarasya pṛthagvibhaktā pralaye ca goptā|| 114.126||
ityevam uktvā vacanaṃ surendrāḥ praṇamya māṃ siddhagaṇāśca hṛṣṭāḥ|
vyapetaśokāḥ pravibhaktasomā gatā vimānairanilogravegāḥ|| 114.127||
ityetat paramaṃ guhyaṃ puṇyāt puṇyataraṃ mahat|
svayaṃ svayambhuvā proktaṃ stotraṃ pāpapraṇāśanam|| 114.128||
yastu dhārayate nityaṃ matparo niyame sthitaḥ|
brahmodgītaṃ śivaṃ hyetat sarvaroganibarhaṇam|| 114.129||
gatiṃ tasya pravakṣyāmi paratreha ca dehinaḥ|
viṣaṃ tasya varārohe sthāvaraṃ jaṅgamaṃ tathā|| 114.130||
saṃprāpya gātraṃ suśroṇi kṣipraṃ sa pratihanyate|
śamam etya śubhaṃ ghoraṃ duḥsvapnaṃ cāpakarṣati|| 114.131||
strīṣu vallabhatāṃ yāti sabhāyāṃ pārthivasya ca|
vivāde jayam āpnoti yuddhe caiva na saṃśayaḥ|| 114.132||
gacchato 'adhvani ca kṣemaṃ sattvaṃ caivopajāyate|
śarīrabhede vakṣyāmi gatiṃ tasya varānane|| 114.133||
hariśmaśrurnīlakaṇṭhaḥ śaśāṅkāṅkitamūrdhajaḥ|
tryakṣo 'abhedyastriśūlī ca vṛṣaketurmahābalaḥ|| 114.134||
nanditulyavapuścaiva nanditulyaparākramaḥ|
vicaratyakhilaṃ siddhaḥ saptalokaṃ mamājñayā|| 114.135||
na hanyate gatistasya vāyoriva nabhastale|
mama pārśvacaro bhūtvā tiṣṭhati ābhūtasamplavam|| 114.136||
ye 'api caitadvarārohe sadā śṛṇvanti mānavāḥ|
teṣāṃ caiva pravakṣyāmi phalaṃ phalasahasrade|| 114.137||
brāhmaṇo vedam āpnoti kṣatriyo vindate mahīm|
vaiśyastu labhate lābhaṃ śūdraḥ prāpnoti sadgatim|| 114.138||
vyādhito mucyate rogādbaddho mucyeta bandhanāt|
gurviṇī janayet putraṃ kanyā vindati satpatim|| 114.139||
naṣṭaṃ ca labhate dravyam iha loke paratra ca|
gavāṃ śatasahasrasya samyagdattasya yat phalam|| 114.140||
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti śrutvā martyaḥ kathām imām|
akṣaraṃ vātha pādaṃ vā ślokaṃ ślokārdham eva vā|| 114.141||
athavā sarvam adhyāyaṃ devabrāhmaṇsasaṃsadi|
yaḥ paṭhenmānavo nityaṃ madgatenāntarātmanā|| 114.142||
śraddadhānaḥ sadodyukto rudraloke mahīyate|
paṭhasva devi bhadraṃ te pāṭhayasva ca bāndhavān|| 114.143||
ataḥ parataraṃ stotraṃ na bhūtaṃ na bhaviṣyati|
nāpi yakṣāḥ piśācā vā na bhūtā na vināyakāḥ|| 114.144||
kuryurvighnaṃ gṛhe tatra yatrāyaṃ tiṣṭhate stavaḥ|
yathā vimuktaṃ kṣetreṣu kṣetraṃ śreṣṭhaṃ prakalpitam|| 114.145||
tathā stavo variṣṭho 'ayaṃ stavānāṃ brahmanirmitaḥ|
yaścainaṃ śrāvayecchrāddhe brāhmaṇān pādam antataḥ|| 114.146||
akṣayyam annapānaṃ vai pitR̥ṃstasyopatiṣṭhati|
manasā cintitaṃ yacca yacca vācāpyudāhṛtam|| 114.147||
sarvaṃ saṃpadyate tasya stavasyāsyānukīrtanāt|
śrutvaitat paramaṃ guhyaṃ ye 'api syuḥ pāpayonayaḥ|| 114.148||
striyaḥ śūdrāśca te 'apīha rudralokaṃ vrajantyuta|
yadā mānuṣyatām eti kadācit kālaparyayāt|| 114.149||
vedavedāṅgatattvajño vimale jāyate kule|
devabhaktaśca bhavati dharmaṃ ca kurute tadā|| 114.150||
itihāsam idaṃ puṇyaṃ sarvakilbiṣanāśanam|
ūktaṃ mayātra tuṣṭhena svayam evāmbujekṣaṇe|| 114.151||
iti skandapurāṇe amṛtamathane nīlakaṇṭhopākhyāne brahmadevakṛtaṃ
mahādevastotraṃ nāma caturdaśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 114.114||

skandapurana115
vyāsa uvāca|
amṛte 'apahṛte tasmin viṣṇunā chadmarūpiṇā|
daityāśca dānavāścaiva kiṃ cakrustadanantaram|| 115.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te krodhādvañcitāḥ sarve viṣṇunā dānaveśvarāḥ|
saṃnahya yuddhāya tadā garhanto viṣṇum ūcire|| 115.2||
dhigbalaṃ dhik ca te śauryaṃ pāpa dhik te parākramam|
viśrambhaghātī nityaṃ tvaṃ nīcakarmā durātmavān|| 115.3||
tvayā nikṛtyā nihato hiraṇyakaśipuḥ purā|
hiraṇyākṣaśca daityendro 'amṛtaṃ cedam apāhṛtam|| 115.4||
na tvāsti balaṃ yuddhe nikṛtyā hi balī bhavān|
yuddhe sthito bhavānastu na no mokṣam avāpsyati|| 115.5||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa daityārāṭ kruddha udgiran pāvakārciṣaḥ|
rathenāmbudanādena viṣṇum evābhidudruve|| 115.6||
vipracitiśca daityendro gajena gajinaṃ tadā|
samāhvayat sahasrākṣaṃ gajinaṃ vajrapāṇinam|| 115.7||
virocanastu saṃkruddho dhaneśaṃ rākṣasādhipam|
gajenaivābhidudrāva jalado bhāskaraṃ yathā|| 115.8||
balirvairocaniścāpi yamaṃ pitṛgaṇādhipam|
rathenaivābhidudrāva vighno vighnam ivāparam|| 115.9||
anuhrādaśca daityendro hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ|
varuṇaṃ prati dudrāva nadīvego yathārṇavam|| 115.10||
mayastu dānavaśreṣṭhastārastāraka eva ca|
ādityaiḥ saha saṃsaktā gajā iva mahāgajaiḥ|| 115.11||
śarabhaḥ śataketuśca balo mūkaśca dānavaḥ|
rudrānevābhyadhāvanta siṃhāḥ siṃhānivājane|| 115.12||
śambhuḥ kārtasvanaścaiva mahāmāyaśca śambaraḥ|
vasubhiḥ saha saṃsaktā vyasanānīva sādhubhiḥ|| 115.13||
narako 'atha hayagrīvastathendradamano 'asuraḥ|
aśvibhyāṃ saha saṃsaktā grahābhyām iva tārakāḥ|| 115.14||
anye cānyaiḥ suraiḥ sārdhaṃ mahāmāyā mahābalāḥ|
āhūyāhūya yudhyante sarve krodhena dānavāḥ|| 115.15||
vipracittirmahāmāyaḥ sahasrākṣaṃ tribhiḥ śaraiḥ|
ardayāmāsa nādena nādayanto diśo daśa|| 115.16||
tasyendraḥ kārmukaṃ citram asyato laghuhastavān|
vajreṇa śatadhāreṇa śatadhā vyabhajadbalī|| 115.17||
tato 'asya gajam ādhore kārmukaṃ gṛhṇato 'aparam|
gajena pothayāmāsa sa papāta yathā giriḥ|| 115.18||
tam āplutaṃ gajāccaiva dānavaṃ devarāḍbalī|
vajreṇātāḍayat krauñcaṃ śaktyā guha ivāhave|| 115.19||
sa tena vajraghātena dānavo mūḍhacetanaḥ|
apatadbhūtale kṣipraṃ vātarugṇa iva drumaḥ|| 115.20||
tato hāhākṛtam abhūddānavānāṃ bale tadā|
sādhu sādhviti devānāṃ siṃhanādāśca bṛṃhitāḥ|| 115.21||
pratilabhya tataḥ saṃjñāṃ sa śaktyā bhīmarūpayā|
mātaṅgaṃ tasya saṃmattam anayadyamasādanam|| 115.22||
tato 'asya pṛṣṭharakṣāṃśca kavacaṃ ca mahāprabham|
śātayāmāsa devāgryaḥ sa hitvā saṃyugaṃ yayau|| 115.23||
baliryamasya puṇḍraṃ ca kṛtāntaṃ kalahaṃ tathā|
kālaṃ ca niyatiṃ caiva kiṃkarān pāśam eva ca|| 115.24||
ekaikaṃ paśyatastīkṣṇaiḥ pañcabhiḥ pañcabhiḥ śaraiḥ|
yamaṃ caiva catuṣṣaṣṭyā hṛdaye samavidhyata|| 115.25||
tasya cānadataḥ kṣipraṃ yamaḥ kruddho hasaṃstadā|
daṇḍena ratham āhatya bhasmasāyujyam ānayat|| 115.26||
hate rathe sasūte tu sāśve saha padānugaiḥ|
tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti saṇnadya yamaṃ baliradhāvata|| 115.27||
tasyāpatata evāśu yamo daṇḍam avāsṛjat|
mūrdhni tena prahāreṇa tataḥ so 'agānmahītalam|| 115.28||
tato hāhākṛtam abhūddānavānāṃ bale tadā|
gṛhṇa gṛhṇeti cāpi ūcuḥ kaṣṭaṃ kaṣṭaṃ tathāpare|| 115.29||
anuhrādastu varuṇaṃ nārācena mahābalaḥ|
āhatya hṛdaye kruddho rathopasthe nyapātayat|| 115.30||
sa utthāya kṣaṇāddevo vikṛṣya balavaddhanuḥ|
sāyakāṃstasya saṃdhārya dhanuściccheda vīryavān|| 115.31||
aśvāñjaghāna sūtasya śiraḥ kāyādapātayat|
tasya praskandataścāpi hatāśvādrathasattamāt|| 115.32||
bibheda hṛdayaṃ śīghraṃ sa papāta yathā mṛtaḥ|
myastārastārakaśca ādityān dṛḍham ārdayan|| 115.33||
te 'api tān virathāṃścakruḥ sarvāñcharaśataistribhiḥ|
śarabhaḥ śataketuśca balo mūkaśca dānavaḥ|| 115.34||
rudrānastrairbahuvidhairnādayanto 'ardayan yudhi|
teṣām astrāṇi tāni sma prativārya mahābalāḥ|| 115.35||
śalabhā iva kedārān muhūrtena vyanāśayan|
te kālyamānāstai rudrairbahubhirvirathāstadā|| 115.36||
raṇaṃ tyaktvā mahāmāyā vipalāyanta sarvaśaḥ|
śambhuḥ kārtasvanaścaiva mahāmāyaśca śambaraḥ|| 115.37||
vasūnabhyadravan yuddhe gajāḥ prati gajāniva|
teṣāṃ tu vasavaḥ sarve svāpanāstraṃ sasarjire|| 115.38||
ratheṣvavasthitā yena babhuḥ suptā yathā mṛgāḥ|
tān suptān rathayantāro raṇāt tasmādapāharan|| 115.39||
haratāṃ caiva sutānām uttamāṅgānyapātayan|
te hateṣvatha sūteṣu udbhrāntairvājibhistadā|| 115.40||
suptā eva raṇe sarve bhrāmyante ditisūnavaḥ|
narako 'atha hayagrīvastathendradamano 'api ca|| 115.41||
aśvinau dvau susaṃyattā yuyudhuste 'asureśvarāḥ|
tān āpatata evātha tau devau bhiṣajāṃ varau|| 115.42||
daṇḍenāstreṇa virathān sarvāneva pracakratuḥ|
punaścāpatataḥ sarvān gadinaḥ krodhamūrchitān|| 115.43||
vāyavyāstreṇa sahasā saṃcikṣipaturāhave|
anye cānyāṃstadā devā ditiputrān vyapothayan|| 115.44||
abhajyantas yathā siṃhairmṛgāraṇye 'abhisaṃhatāḥ|
prahlādaścāpi daityendro viṣṇunā saha saṃgataḥ|| 115.45||
mahat kṛtvā tadā yuddhaṃ virathaḥ samapadyata|
sa cakreṇa hatāśvastu hatasūtapadānugaḥ|| 115.46||
gadāṃ gṛhītvā praskandya janārdanam upādravat|
tasyodyatakandarasyātha dhāvataśca mahāmune|| 115.47||
ciccheda tāṃ gadām āśu cakreṇaiva janārdanaḥ|
atha te dānavāḥ śūraistairdevairbhagnavikramāḥ|| 115.48||
abhajyanta yathā siṃhairvane mṛgagaṇā bhayāt|
tān bhagnān bhajyamānāṃśca dṛṣṭvā tyaktvā raṇaṃ yayuḥ|| 115.49||
prahlādo 'api raṇaṃ tyaktvā tānevānujagāma ha|
teṣu bhagneṣvathendrasya jayaśabdaṃ supūjitam|| 115.50||
samaṃ cakrustadā devāḥ sanārāyaṇalokāpāḥ|
siṃhanādāṃśca vividhān vāditrāṇi nyavādayan|| 115.51||
iti skandapurāṇe amṛtamathane yuddhe pañcadaśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ||
115||

skandapurana116
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ tadabhavadvyāsa amṛtasyāvamanthanam|
yuddhaṃ ca sumahāghoraṃ prahlādena sahaiva tu|| 116.1||
sa tu kālena mahatā kṛtvā yuddhaśatānyuta|
putre virocane rājyaṃ pradadāvasureśvaraḥ|| 116.2||
virocanaḥ punarvyāsa rājyasyārthe mahābalaḥ|
āṭībake hato yuddhe devendreṇa mahaujasā|| 116.3||
vyāsa uvāca|
āṭībakaḥ sa saṃgrāmaḥ katham āsīnmahābhayaḥ|
śrotum icchāmi bhagavan paraṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me|| 116.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
babhūva punareveha devānām asuraiḥ saha|
sakhyaṃ te dadṛśuścaiva dūrādvai vismitānanāḥ|| 116.5||
ghorām ilāvṛte tasmin varṣe vikṛtarūpiṇīm|
ugrām ātharvaṇīṃ kṛtyām asurāṇāṃ bhayaṃkarīm|| 116.6||
tāṃ dṛṣṭvā te 'abruvan keyam āṭirityeva devatāḥ|
asurā baka ityeva vivādaścāpyajāyata|| 116.7||
sāpi kṛtyā tadā ghorā devebhyo darśanaṃ dadau|
āṭirityeva teṣāṃ ca asurāṇāṃ bako 'abhavat|| 116.8||
teṣāṃ paṇo 'abhavat tatra rājyaṃ prati mahāmune|
yo no jitaḥ sa no dāso jetā svāmī bhavatviti|| 116.9||
tataḥ sā hi āṭirūpeṇa sarvebhyo darśanaṃ dadau|
tataste vijitā devān procurnā sma jitā iti|| 116.10||
baka evaiṣa suvyaktaṃ jitā yūyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ|
na yam āṭirbako 'ayaṃ vai na bakaścāṭireva hi|| 116.11||
evaṃ vivadatāṃ yuddham abhavadrājyakāraṇāt|
teṣāṃ dānavamukhyānāṃ devaiḥ saha bhayāvaham|| 116.12||
varṣāṇāṃ vai sahasraṃ tu hato yatra virocanaḥ|
hate virocane brahmā baliṃ teṣāṃ mahāsuram|| 116.13||
abhyaṣecayadindratve sa ca rājā babhūva ha|
tataḥ sa lokāṃstrīn vyāsa balenākrāmadavyayaḥ|| 116.14||
trailokyasyeśvaraścaiva sa jajñe hyasureśvaraḥ|
jitvā yuddhena devendraṃ sthānādacyāvayat prabhuḥ|| 116.15||
indratvam akaroccaiva yamatvaṃ ca mahābalaḥ|
sa eva varuṇaścābhūddhaneśo 'agnistathaiva ca|| 116.16||
ādityaścaiva somaśca parjanyo vṛṣṭisarjanaḥ|
sarvaṃ jagati kartavyaṃ sa eva kurute sadā|| 116.17||
evaṃ śāsati vai rājyaṃ devānām asukhaṃ tadā|
bhraṣṭaiśvaryā mahātmāno bhramanti śakunā iva|| 116.18||
teṣāṃ brahmā dadau buddhiṃ duḥkhitānāṃ mahātmanām|
āśvāsya bahudhā vyāsa kāruṇyāddevasattamaḥ|| 116.19||
brahmovāca|
devā na śakyo yuṣmābhirbalireṣa prabādhitum|
mahātmā dhārmikaścāyam amaraśca na saṃśayaḥ|| 116.20||
brahmaṇyaśca balīyāṃśca tathā labdhavaraśca ha|
taṃ gatvā viprarūpeṇa viṣṇureṣa prayācatu|| 116.21||
vāmanaṃ rūpam āsthāya bhūmervai vikramatrayam|
dāsyate sa gṛhītvā tat kramatām eṣa sarvaśaḥ|| 116.22||
bhūmiṃ kramasamāṃ sarvaṃ kariṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|
kramaṃ dvitīyaṃ dhātāsya antarikṣe tataḥ svayam|| 116.23||
ahaṃ caiva pradāsyāmi tṛtīyaṃ kramam ityuta|
evaṃ vo rājyalābho 'ayaṃ dṛśyate nānyathā surāḥ|| 116.24||
yasmin kāle prakramate viṣṇureṣa triviṣṭapam|
tasmin kāle ca rakṣadhvaṃ sarvayatnena dānavān|| 116.25||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te evam uktā deveśā niścitya bahudhā śubham|
viṣṇum ūcurmahāsattvāḥ kriyatāṃ brahmaṇo vacaḥ|| 116.26||
dīkṣitaścāsuraśreṣṭho hayamedhena so 'adya vai|
kalyaṃ cāvabhṛthaṃ tasya gatvā yācasva taṃ prabho|| 116.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam astviti tenoktā devā yuddhāya daṃśitāḥ|
atiṣṭhanta tadā sarve śakraṃ kṛtvā puraḥsaram|| 116.28||
nārado 'atha tadā gatvā pūjitastena bhaktitaḥ|
sukhopaviṣṭaḥ prāhedaṃ vacanaṃ vadatāṃ varaḥ|| 116.29||
dharmeṇa tava tuṣṭo 'aham ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
anāsuram idaṃ vṛttaṃ tava dānavasattama|| 116.30||
sarve hi dānavāḥ krūrā brahmaghnā lokakaṇṭakāḥ|
tvaṃ tu brāhmaṇabhaktaśca lokānāṃ hitakṛt tathā|| 116.31||
tasmāt tava śubhaṃ cintyaṃ sadaivāsurapuṃgava|
yathā ca te śubhaṃ kiṃcit syādrājan nityam eva hi|| 116.32||
eṣa devaiḥ praṇihito viṣṇurvipratvam āsthitaḥ|
trīṃstvāṃ rājyārtham udyuktaḥ prārthayiṣyati vikramān|| 116.33||
tanna tasya tvayā deyaṃ rājyaṃ paścānna te bhavet|
ataḥ paraṃ bhavān rājan pramāṇam asureśvara|| 116.34||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā balirvairocanistadā|
uvāca praṇato vyāsa nāradaṃ dānaveśvaraḥ|| 116.35||
śatravaste mama dṛḍhaṃ teṣāṃ cāhaṃ mahāmune|
yadi te māṃ prayācante kṛtārtho 'asmi tato nanu|| 116.36||
svadharmaṃ saṃparityajya yadi cenmadhusūdanaḥ|
māṃ prayācati dīnātmā saphalaṃ jīvitaṃ mama|| 116.37||
vrataṃ cedaṃ mama brahman sadaiva hi mahāmune|
yācito na dadāmīti na vadeyam iti prabho|| 116.38||
ūrdhvaṃ praṇā hyutkrāmanti yācato viprasattama|
bruvato na dadāmīti narakāyotkramantyatha|| 116.39||
dehīti ruditasyākhyā nāstīti pratirodanā|
mā māṃ nārada paśyantu rudantam itare janāḥ|| 116.40||
eṣā bhavati sarvasya puruṣasya mahāmune|
yācato mama dātāyam icchā taddhyakṣayaṃ phalam|| 116.41||
so 'ahaṃ yadi na dāsyāmi śatrubhyo yācitaṃ mahat|
narakaṃ rauravaṃ nāma pratipatsyāmyasaṃśayam|| 116.42||
yo hi vai yācamānāya na dadāti narādhamaḥ|
sa taṃ hinasti yācantam āśācchedānna saṃśayaḥ|| 116.43||
bhavān mama pitā vyaktaṃ putraḥ snehakṛto hyaham|
nāhaṃ na dāsye viprendra nirvṛtiste bhavatviyam|| 116.44||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa taṃ tadāmantrya tena caiva supūjitaḥ|
divam akrāmadavyagraścintayānaḥ kathaṃ bhavet|| 116.45||
gate 'atha tasmin divase rajanyāṃ sa mahāyaśāḥ|
viṣṇurvāmanarūpeṇa vipro bhūtvā tam arthayat|| 116.46||
sa cāpi rājā viprendra ratnāni ca vasūni ca|
grāmān dāsīśca mahiṣīrgavāśvān rathahastinaḥ|| 116.47||
vāhanāni ca citrāṇi suvarṇaṃ śayanāni ca|
śayyāstaraṇavastrāṇi bhūṣaṇāni gṛhāṇi ca|| 116.48||
yaṃ yam arthayate vipro yāvadyaśca yathā yathā|
tathā tathā sa daityendro dadātyevāvicārayan|| 116.49||
taṃ tathā vartamānaṃ tu vāmanaḥ sumahāyaśāḥ|
prāha mahyaṃ prayacchasva yadahaṃ prabravīmi te|| 116.50||
sa tam argheṇa pādyena āsanādibhireva ca|
saṃpūjyaivābravīdbrūhi yat taveṣṭaṃ dvijottama|| 116.51||
vāmana uvāca|
yadi prayacchase rājan yācamānāya kāmataḥ|
tato bravīmyanyathā tu na vakṣyāmyasureśvara|| 116.52||
baliruvāca|
jñātvārthaṃ pratijānīyāṃ deyaṃ brāhmaṇa tadyadi|
dātuṃ ca śakyaṃ tat syāt tu tato 'ahaṃ dātum utsahe|| 116.53||
vāmana uvāca|
pratijñā bhavato nityam iyaṃ hyasurasattama|
yadyat prayācate vipro dadyāṃ tat tadahaṃ tviti|| 116.54||
dīkṣitaścāśvamedhena tvaṃ dadāsyasurādhipa|
yadyat prayācate viprastat taddatse na saṃśayaḥ|| 116.55||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto niścitya punarevāha taṃ nṛpaḥ|
prahasya sumahāvīryam idaṃ vacanakovidaḥ|| 116.56||
baliruvāca|
bhavān viṣṇurviprarūpī chadmanā māṃ prayācase|
kṣatradharmaṃ samutsṛjya kārpaṇyaṃ ca prabhāṣase|| 116.57||
dīnānām api sarveṣām ahaṃ dadyāṃ prayācitaḥ|
rājyaṃ vinā hi devāya tubhyaṃ dāsye yathepsitam|| 116.58||
vāmana uvāca|
satyam etadahaṃ viṣṇurhṛtarājyā vayaṃ tvayā|
na rājye 'adya spṛhāsmākaṃ niḥspṛhā hi tato vayam|
gṛhaṃ tvāṃ saṃprayācāma yatra vatsyāmi nirvṛtaḥ|| 116.59||
baliruvāca|
kiṃ pramāṇaṃ gṛhaṃ tadvai prayācasi sureśvara|
kīdṛśaṃ kva ca taddāsye brūhi vāmana sarvaśaḥ|| 116.60||
vāmana uvāca|
sarvabhūmiguṇairyuktaṃ yatra tatra mahāgṛham|
mama kramaistribhiryuktaṃ datsva rājan gṛhārthine|| 116.61||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha śukrastadā vyāsa baliṃ prāha mahātapāḥ|
na dātavyaṃ mahārāja viṣṇureṣa mahābalaḥ|| 116.62||
ayaṃ sa hantā sarveṣaṃ dānavānāṃ durāsadaḥ|
chadmanaivam ihāyāto viṣṇurenaṃ visarjaya|| 116.63||
anādṛtya vacastasya provāca ditinandanaḥ|
dāsye tubhyaṃ gṛhaṃ viṣṇo yādṛśaṃ tvaṃ prayācase|| 116.64||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā provāca madhusūdanaḥ|
baliṃ rājānam anaghaṃ sarveṣām eva saṃnidhau|| 116.65||
vāmana uvāca|
sādhyo devo 'aham anagha dharmaputro diteḥ suta|
tataḥ pratigrahe doṣo na mamāsti mahābala|| 116.66||
yadi deyaṃ gṛhaṃ madhyaṃ paścāt tāpo na te yadi|
haste mama jalaṃ rājan pātayasvāsureśvara|| 116.67||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bāḍham ityuktvā bhṛṅgāreṇa mahābalaḥ|
pradātum upacakrāma vāmanāya gṛhaṃ mahat|| 116.68||
atha te dānavāḥ krūrāḥ pratiṣedhanalālasāḥ|
ājagmurbhṛśam āyattā baliṃ prati mahāmune|| 116.69||
prahlādo bhrātṛbhiḥ sārdhaṃ mayo jambho 'ardhalocaḥ|
vipracittiśca vikrāntaḥ anye ca sumahābalāḥ|| 116.70||
ūcuste taṃ tadā gatvā kṛtvā prahlādam agrataḥ|
baliṃ vairocaniṃ vyāsa cintayantaḥ parābhavam|| 116.71||
prahlāda uvāca|
kim idaṃ putra durbuddhe tvayā vyavasitaṃ mahat|
nāśanaṃ ditiputrāṇāṃ naitat kāryaṃ mahābala|| 116.72||
viṣṇureṣa mahāmāyo durātmā daityaghātakaḥ|
lokatrayam api hyeṣa kramiṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|| 116.73||
tvam asmākaṃ gatiḥ putra tvaṃ vīryaṃ tvaṃ parākramaḥ|
tvayi jīvitam āyattaṃ mā naḥ kṣipraṃ vināśaya|| 116.74||
hiraṇyakaśipuu rājā hiraṇyākṣaśca dānavaḥ|
tava rājñaḥ kalāṃ putra nārdhataḥ ṣoḍaśīm api|| 116.75||
maitasya vibudhasya tvaṃ gṛhaṃ datsva bravīmyaham|
etaddhi śreyaḥ sarveṣāṃ tava caiva mahābala|| 116.76||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā prahlādasya mahātmanaḥ|
baliḥ praṇamya dharmātmā idam āha mahāyaśāḥ|| 116.77||
baliruvāca|
jāne 'ahaṃ vibudho 'ayaṃ vai viṣṇuḥ sarvāsurāntakaḥ|
pratijñaiva mameyaṃ hi dātavyaṃ yācitena me|| 116.78||
ahaṃ dānapatiḥ khyātastriṣu lokeṣu viśrutaḥ|
kathaṃ tadanyathā kuryāṃ jīvite sati dānavāḥ|| 116.79||
adharmyam ayasyaṃ ca asvargyaṃ bhayadaṃ mahat|
kathaṃ nāmānṛtaṃ kuryām iti me vratam āhitam|
pratiśrutya kathaṃ bhūyo 'asurāste dharmakāraṇāt|| 116.80||
prahlāda uvāca|
dānavānāṃ sadaityānāṃ putra dharmaḥ svayaṃ kṛtaḥ|
adharmeṇa hi vardhante sadaiva ditidānavāḥ|| 116.81||
māyā caivānṛtaṃ caiva dambhaḥ sarvavadhastathā|
yajñānāṃ parimoṣaśca dharma eṣa hi naḥ śubhaḥ|| 116.82||
sa tvaṃ pratiśrutya vibho mā dadasva durātmane|
tathā hi no bhavedvṛddhiranyatheha bhayaṃ mahat|| 116.83||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā balirniścintya buddhimān|
uvācāsuraśārdūla idaṃ vacanakovidaḥ|| 116.84||
baliruvāca|
ya eṣa dharmo 'adharmeṇa bhavadbhiḥ saṃpracoditaḥ|
na hyasya phalam ānantyaṃ krūrasyāsurasattama|| 116.85||
hiraṇyakaśipuu rājā nāntyantaṃ sukham āptavān|
hiraṇyākṣastathā caiva andhakaścaiva tatsutaḥ|| 116.86||
bhavān pitāmaho 'asmākaṃ tathā krūreṇa karmaṇā|
tasmānnedaṃ praśaṃsanti ye kecidviduṣo janāḥ|| 116.87||
ṛṣayaḥ paśya satyena dharmeṇa divi saṃsthitāḥ|
devā jayanti cātyarthaṃ grahā divyanti caiva hi|| 116.88||
na kaściddṛśyate vyomni tathā krūreṇa karmaṇā|
prasādayan kṣāmaye tvāṃ bravīmi ditijeśvara|| 116.89||
prahlāda uvāca|
duṣṭaṃ vāpyathavā krūraṃ śobhanaṃ vāpi dānava|
svakarma na vimoktavyaṃ pāramparyāgataṃ mahat|| 116.90||
-- -- -- pitṛbhiścaiva tathā caiva pitāmahaiḥ|
ācīrṇaṃ putra naitat te vimoktavyaṃ mahāmune|| 116.91||
baliruvāca|
pitṛbhirhi yathā cīrṇaṃ kartavyaṃ yadaśaṅkitaiḥ|
garhitaṃ yat satāṃ cāpi pitāmaha śṛṇuṣva me|| 116.92||
āsīdṛṣiradīnātmā vāmadeva iti śrutaḥ|
tasya dṛṣṭvorvaśīṃ mohādretaḥskando babhūva ha|| 116.93||
tadbhūmāvaviddhaṃ vai cakhāda vaḍavā kila|
tasyā garbhaḥ samabhavat sadyaḥ so 'aśvatarī bhavat|| 116.94||
tām ṛṣiḥ sa sutasnehāt pupoṣa bahulāḥ samāḥ|
athāgāt tatra rājarṣiraṣṭako nāma vīryavān|| 116.95||
sa tām apaśyadrājendra ṛṣerāśramamadhyagām|
acintayaddhṛdā caiva idaṃ paramaharṣitaḥ|| 116.96||
mama patnyāstu sadṛśī iyaṃ lakṣaṇasampadā|
yadi dadyādimāṃ vipraḥ syādagraṃ mama saṃgatam|| 116.97||
na cāyaṃ dāsyate vipro mahyam enāṃ sudurlabhām|
upāyaṃ tu kariṣyāmi yena dāsyati suprabhām|| 116.98||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa rājā taṃ gatvā vāmadevam uvāca ha|
praṇamya bahumānena nikṛtyā śaktinandana|| 116.99||
rājovāca|
aśvataryānayā kāryaṃ mama kiṃcinmahāmune|
saṃvatsaraṃ susaṃpūrṇaṃ prayacchasva prayācitaḥ|| 116.100||
pariprāpte punaḥ kṛtye tubhyaṃ vai dvijasattama|
punaḥ pradāsye viprendra yadi deyā pradīyatām|| 116.101||
tataḥ sa ṛṣiśārdūlastasmai prādādaninditām|
tāṃ gṛhītvā yayau rājā labheti hṛṣitastadā|| 116.102||
atha saṃvatsare pūrṇe tam āha ṛṣisattamaḥ|
tam uvāca tato vipraḥ prayacchāśvatarīṃ śubhām|| 116.103||
na dadau sa hi durbuddhirṛṣiḥ krodhājjaghāna tam|
tasya putrastato rājā babhūva narapuṃgavaḥ|| 116.104||
tam api āha tato vipro na dadau sa ca tāṃ tadā|
tato mamāra so 'apyevaṃ viprakrodhāddurātmavān|| 116.105||
tasya putro 'abhavaccaiva rājā ditijasattamaḥ|
tam uvāca tato vipraḥ prayacchāśvatarīm iti|| 116.106||
atha so 'api tathā kṛtvā yācitaḥ sudurātmavān|
uvāca nāhaṃ dāsyāmi pitṛhantre durātmane|| 116.107||
tatastam apyasau kruddho vipraḥ prāṇairvyayojayat|
tato bālaḥ sutastasya rājābhavadatidyutiḥ|| 116.108||
tam apyasau tathā vipraḥ provāca krodhamūrchitaḥ|
nāśayiṣye kulaṃ tadvai aṣṭakasya durātmanaḥ|| 116.109||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bālaḥ saṃpūjya taṃ dvijam|
uvāca sacivān dṛṣṭvā paścāddāsyāmi vāḍavām|| 116.110||
sacivān sa tadānāyya apṛcchaddānaveśvara|
iyam aśvatarī brūta dātavyā neti vā śubhā|| 116.111||
sacivā ūcuḥ|
pitāmahasya te pitrā iyam aśvatarī purā|
varṣam ekaṃ prayācyeha samānītā nareśvara|| 116.112||
pūrṇe varṣe tu viprasya yācato 'api mahāmune|
na dattā sa ca kopena viprasyāsya mamāra ha|| 116.113||
tataḥ pitāmahastubhyam āsīdrājā prajeśvara|
tathaiva so 'apyadatvaināṃ viprakrodhānmamāra ha|| 116.114||
bhavāṃstu yadi pūrveṣāṃ vṛttaṃ samanuvartate|
na deyā viprarūpasya mṛtyorasya durātmanaḥ|| 116.115||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā sacivānāṃ pramanyumān|
nirbhatsya tānadharmajñānidam āha mahātapāḥ|| 116.116||
pūrve te maurkhyam āsthāya kṛtavanto 'atidāruṇam|
adharmyam ayaśasyaṃ ca sadbhiścaiva vigarhitam|| 116.117||
ahaṃ na teṣāṃ panthānam anuvarte kathaṃcana|
adya tānakṛtaprajñān pitR̥nnatha pitāmahān|| 116.118||
gartasthāṃstārayiṣyāmi kulaṃ ca sumahat tathā|
ityuktvā nidhane teṣāṃ jātaḥ putro mahāmatiḥ|| 116.119||
viprasyāśvatarīdāne matiṃ cakre suniścitām|
tatastam ṛṣim abhyarcya gandhamālyādibhirnṛpaḥ|| 116.120||
tāṃścaivāśvatarīṃ prādādātmīyāṃ sa narādhipaḥ|
vasu caiva hi datvāsmai ṛṣiṃ taṃ sa prasādayat|| 116.121||
tataḥ sa ṛṣiśārdūlaḥ prahṛṣṭenāntarātmanā|
utthāpya rājaśārdūlam idam āha tadā vibhuḥ|| 116.122||
tvayā tīrṇāḥ suputreṇa pitaraḥ sapitāmahāḥ|
narakasthā mahābāho brāhmaṇasvena veṣṭitāḥ|| 116.123||
na kṛtyaṃ mama ratnaiśca nāśvataryā narādhipa|
tuṣṭastubhyaṃ prayacchāmi sarvam etannarādhipa|| 116.124||
yadyaṣṭako mamaivaṃ vai kṛtavān syāddurātmavān|
tatputro vā mahābāho pitā vā tava durmatiḥ|| 116.125||
vināśaṃ na gatāste syurahaṃ tuṣṭaśca sarvaśaḥ|
tadāpṛcche gamiṣyāmi tavaiṣā dravyam eva ca|| 116.126||
tataḥ sa ṛṣiśārdūlo jagāma vanam eva hi|
rājāpyaśvatarīṃ labdhvā tayā reme yathāsukham|| 116.127||
evaṃ hi na praśaṃsanti pūrveṣāṃ dharmavarjitam|
karma sarve dvijā rājan ye cānye dharmavādinaḥ|
tasmāddāsyāmyahaṃ rājyaṃ vāmanāya mahātmane|| 116.128||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ so 'asuraśārdūlo vāmanasya tadā kare|
pātayāmāsa vidhivajjalaṃ paramapūjitam|| 116.129||
tasya pātitamātre tu jale viṣṇormahātmanaḥ|
daityendrasyopari tadā puṣpavṛṣṭiḥ papāta ha|| 116.130||
sādhu sādhviti bhūtānām adṛśyānāṃ ca nisvanaḥ|
devadundubhayaścātra svayaṃ neduranāhatāḥ|| 116.131||
marutaśca śubhān gandhān ādāya pravavuḥ śubhāḥ|
hatāḥ stha dānavāḥ sarve iti cātrābhavat svanaḥ|| 116.132||
tat karma tasyātisuduṣkaraṃ tadā samīkṣya sarve ṛṣayastapodhanāḥ|
praśaṃsamānā ditinandaneśvaraṃ praṇemurārānmadhusūdanaṃ tadā|| 116.133||
iti skandapurāṇe vāmane ṣoḍaśottaraśato .adhyāyaḥ|| 116.116||

skandapurana117
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavān viṣṇuruvācāsurapuṃgavam|
kramāmi vikramaiḥ paśya dānaveśvara suprabha|| 117.1||
yadi cet pūryate dattaṃ na ceddātavya ityuta|
bhavatā bhūmibhāgo 'anyaḥ satyavāgbhava dānava|| 117.2||
baliruvāca|
kramasva vāmanaśreṣṭha kramāṃstrīnadya sarvaśaḥ|
na cet pūryeta dātāhaṃ satyam etadbravīmi te|| 117.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa devadeveśaṃ mahādevam umāpatim|
praṇeme parayā bhaktyā kramiṣyan viṣṇuravyayaḥ|| 117.4||
tato devāḥ susaṃyattāḥ saṃnaddhā yuddhalālasāḥ|
ākāśena mahāsattvāstatrājagmurmahābalāḥ|| 117.5||
tataḥ sa puṣkaradvīpe viṣṇuḥ paramadīptimat|
rūpaṃ kṛtvā bhuvaṃ dyāṃ ca -- -- vai kramam ācarat|| 117.6||
sa pādam udaye kṛtvā dvitīyaṃ saritāṃ patau|
puṣkarasyaivottaratastena lokam imaṃ gataḥ|| 117.7||
kramitvā vikramaṃ caikapādam utkṣipatastadā|
ajako nāma daityendraḥ pādaṃ taṃ samagṛhṇata|| 117.8||
sa taṃ sahaivāsureṇa utkṣipan madhusūdanaḥ|
kṣipto 'asāvasuro vyāsa adyāpi na nivartate|| 117.9||
tato dvitīyaṃ rudrasya yogaṃ paramam āsthitaḥ|
antarikṣe bhuvarloka eka eva kramo 'abhavat|| 117.10||
tato 'antarikṣādbhūyo 'api brahmaṇo yogam āsthitaḥ|
svarlokam akhilaṃ vyāsa kramam ekaṃ cakāra ha|| 117.11||
taṃ tu lokaṃ samāsādya niḥsṛtaṃ devasattamaḥ|
janalokaṃ samāsādyana samāptaṃ ca tat tataḥ|| 117.12||
tasya cotkramatastatra daityāḥ śastrāstrapāṇayaḥ|
abhyakramanta vegena devāstān saṃnyavārayan|| 117.13||
daśa putrasahasrāṇi tanayānāṃ balestadā|
yudhyamānā hatāstena vividhāyudhapāṇayaḥ|| 117.14||
bāṇo vātaśca dvāvetau baliputrau mahābalau|
tasmādbhraṣṭau tadā vyāsa saṃgrāmādyayaturmune|| 117.15||
atha brahmā tadābhyetya samayaṃ pracakāra ha|
vimucya pāśāddeveśa imaṃ lokapitāmahaḥ|| 117.16||
bale tvayākhilaṃ rājyaṃ devānāṃ pratipāditam|
satye tvaṃ samaye sthitvā mā rājyaṃ kāmayeḥ punaḥ|| 117.17||
yāvanmanvantaram idam eṣa te samayaḥ śubhaḥ|
paripālyaḥ sadā vatsa gaccha caiva yathāsukham|| 117.18||
idaṃ yajñaphalaṃ samyagavāpsyasi na saṃśayaḥ|
yogaṃ ca matprasādena bhūya eva hyavāpsyasi|| 117.19||
saiva muktastam āpṛcchya pātālaṃ saṃviveśa ha|
devā api tataḥ prāpya svaṃ rājyaṃ mumudurbhṛśam|| 117.20||
vyāsa uvāca|
kīdṛk sa bhagavān viṣṇustyaktvā svaṃ dharmam ūrjitam|
pratyāharata trailokyaṃ na caivāsyānayo 'abhavat|| 117.21||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
kramatastasya devasya viṣṇordīptānalaprabham|
babhau rūpam atīvograṃ durnirīkṣyaṃ surairapi|| 117.22||
atha devāḥ sahendreṇa viṣṇuṃ paramadaivatam|
tuṣṭuvuḥ praśaśaṃsuśca kṛtakṛtyā mahābalam|| 117.23||
prītyā paramayā yuktāḥ sarve divyāstradhāriṇaḥ|
dānavairadyamānānām asmākaṃ vibudheśvaraḥ|| 117.24||
trātā rājyapradaścaiva tvam abhūḥ surasattama|
tvayā sma sukhinaḥ sarve karmiṇaḥ sukṛtairyathā|| 117.25||
tava deva prabhāveṇa rājyaṃ bhokṣyāma vijvarāḥ|
tapanasya prabhāveṇa yathā pūrvaṃ suretarāḥ|| 117.26||
tvaṃ hi naḥ paramaṃ dhāma tathaiva ca parā gatiḥ|
paraṃ pavitraṃ tvaṃ caiva ṛte devam umāpatim|| 117.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyaivaṃ stūyamānasya tridaśaiḥ śārṅgadhanvanaḥ|
abhūt tuṣṭistadātyarthaṃ bahumānastathātmani|| 117.28||
tato 'abhimānatastasya sa yogaḥ paramo mune|
abhraśyata yathā vahniḥ salilena samukṣitaḥ|| 117.29||
tatastadantaraṃ labdhvā pāpmā sā hi āsurī mune|
prahṛṣṭā saṃprahṛṣyainam āviveśa janārdanam|| 117.30||
sa tayā pāpmayā vyāsa āviṣṭo viṣṇuravyayaḥ|
na babhau dīptimāṃstatra santaḥ prāpyeva dāruṇam|| 117.31||
iti skandapurāṇe vāmane trailokyakramaṇe saptadaśottaraśatatamo
.adhyāyaḥ|| 117.117||

skandapurana118
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tathā sa pāpmayā vyāsa āsuryā saṃgatastadā|
tadeva rūpaṃ saṃprāpto vāmanaṃ devasattamaḥ|| 118.1||
taṃ tathā vartamānaṃ tu devāḥ sarve savāsavāḥ|
abruvan kim idaṃ deva tava vaikṛtam īdṛśam|| 118.2||
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā ṛṣayaḥ śaṃsitavratāḥ|
marīcirbhṛguratriśca aṅgirāḥ kratureva ca|| 118.3||
vasiṣṭhaśca pulastyaśca pulaho rucireva ca|
viśvāmitro vāmadevo bharadvājastathauśijaḥ|| 118.4||
gautamaśca śaradvāṃśca kaśyapaścoddalastathā|
vatsāro naidhruvaśca cyavanaścātmavānapi|| 118.5||
dadhīcaśca ṛcīkaśca jamadagniśca viśrutaḥ|
jāmadagnyastathā rāmo hyagastiśca mahātapāḥ|| 118.6||
bṛhaspatiśca śukaśca śaktiśca saparāśaraḥ|
kuṇiśca kuṇibāhaśca tathā sārasvataśca yaḥ|| 118.7||
ete cānye ca ṛṣayo nāradaḥ saparvataḥ|
ūcurdevāṃstadā vyāsa brahmaṇā saṃpracoditāḥ|| 118.8||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ|
vayaṃ devādya saṃprāptā brahmalokāt sureśvarāḥ|
ājñaptā brahmaṇā kṣipraṃ devasyāsya kṛtena ha|| 118.9||
yadanena parityajya svadharmaṃ devabandhunā|
pratigrahaḥ kṛto rājyaṃ vaikuṇṭhena mahātmanā|| 118.10||
tataḥ pāpmāsurāṇāṃ yā sarvaprāṇibhayaṃkarī|
sāsurān saṃparityajya keśavaṃ saṃviveśa ha|| 118.11||
tayābhibhūto devo 'ayam aśaktaḥ śatrubādhane|
na cāsya tejaḥ sarve vai paśyadhvaṃ pūrvavacchubham|| 118.12||
sa eṣa yadi manyadhvaṃ tīrtheṣu susamāhitaḥ|
snātvāśvamedhena punaryajatāṃ daivataiḥ saha|| 118.13||
tataḥ pinākinaṃ dṛṣṭvā tena pūtaśca sarvaśaḥ|
bhavitā pāpmayā mukta evam āha pitāmahaḥ|| 118.14||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste sahitāḥ sarve devā munijanaiḥ saha|
tīrthayātrām akurvaṃstaṃ gṛhītvā viṣṇum avyayam|| 118.15||
te tu puṣkariṇo ramyāṃ suṣumṇeti suviśrutām|
nalinīvanasaṃchannāṃ prahṛṣṭāṇḍajanāditām|| 118.16||
bahuvṛkṣavanopetāṃ phullapaṅkajaśobhitām|
bahūpavanavṛkṣāḍhyāṃ sūkṣmakāñcanavālukām|| 118.17||
vajravaidūryanīlāṅkām indranīlalatopalām|
vividhāṇḍajaśabdāḍhyāṃ siddhacāraṇasevitām|| 118.18||
kiṃnarodgītamadhurām apsarobhiśca sevitām|
mattabhramaragītāḍhyāṃ śrīniketananiketanām|| 118.19||
yasyāṃ snātvā naro martyaḥ svaśarīreṇa suvrata|
vimānenārkabhāsena gacchanti hyamarālayam|| 118.20||
tām āsādya tadā devāḥ suṣumnām ṛṣibhiḥ saha|
padmāni jagṛhuścaiva mṛṇālāni bisāni ca|| 118.21||
atha tatra mahāpadmaṃ vikacaṃ sumanoharam|
sahasrapattrasaṃchannam agastyoddhṛtya gṛhya tat|| 118.22||
tasyāstīre nicikṣepa tataḥ sasnau yathāsukham|
jagrāha tacca devendro 'adṛṣṭaḥ kenacidvibhuḥ|| 118.23||
athāgastyaḥ samuttīrṇo na tat padmam apaśyata|
sarvāṃśca tānupāmantrya idam āha mahāmanāḥ|| 118.24||
agastya uvāca|
mama padmaṃ mahaddevāḥ kenādattaṃ supuṣpitam|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatasta ṛṣayaḥ sarve devāścāpi ṛṣestadā|
prayatnān vividhāṃścakrurekaikaśyena suvrata|| 118.25||
indra uvāca|
sa yajñairyajatām iṣṭairbahubhiścāptadakṣiṇaiḥ|
vaset svarge ca niyataṃ yaste harati paṅkajam|| 118.26||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste menire sarve devendreṇa mahātmanā|
gṛhītaṃ paṅkajaṃ vyāsa indraścainam uvāca ha|| 118.27||
indra uvāca|
ṛṣīṇāṃ dharmatattvāni śṛṇuyāya vayaṃ katham|
upāyo 'ayaṃ kṛtastasmādgṛhāṇedaṃ jalodbhavam|| 118.28||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste tatra saṃpūjya agnīn devān pitR̥nnapi|
brāhmaṇāṃstarpayitvā ca viṣṇoḥ kṛtvā tathāśiṣaḥ|| 118.29||
jagmuranyāni tīrthāni supuṇyāni śubhāni ca|
bahūni vyāsa munayo devāśca susamāhitāḥ|| 118.30||
athāpaśyanta te vṛkṣam ekaṃ śuṣkaṃ mahātarum|
koṭare ca śukaṃ tasya śuṣyantaṃ vyākulendriyam|| 118.31||
te dṛṣṭvā tam apṛcchanta mahendreṇa divaukasaḥ|
divyena cakṣuṣā dṛṣṭvā śukaṃ tuṣṭvā yaśasvinaḥ|| 118.32||
indra uvāca|
khageśvara mṛte hyasmin kasmāt tiṣṭhasi pādape|
apuṣpaphalapattre tvaṃ śuṣke nirupajīvite|| 118.33||
śuka uvāca|
eṣa vṛkṣaḥ purā hi āsīt sumahān kalpavṛkṣavat|
phalairamṛtakalpaiśca ciraścāpyupajīvitaḥ|| 118.34||
daśām imāṃ punaḥ prāptaḥ kālena ca vanaspatiḥ|
jahyādenaṃ kathaṃ prājñaḥ kṛtajño mādṛśaḥ punaḥ|| 118.35||
kṛtaghnaḥ syām ahaṃ deva mṛtam enaṃ parityajan|
ye lokā hyasya vṛkṣasya te me santu śacīpate|| 118.36||
indra uvāca|
prajñāvānasi medhāvī mahātmā nayatattvavit|
kathaṃ mūḍham ivātmānaṃ karoṣi khagapārthiva|| 118.37||
vanaspatirayaṃ sādho dharma eṣo 'asya nityadā|
abuddhipūrvaṃ pakṣīndra svabhāvāccātra kāritaḥ|| 118.38||
nāsyeyaṃ buddhirabhavadvayāṃsi mayi nityaśaḥ|
vasantu mama khādantu phalāni ca yathāsukham|| 118.39||
acetano yathā hyagnirāpo vāyuśca tattvataḥ|
bhūtānām upakārāya svabhāvānnānyathā hi te|| 118.40||
tadvat tvaṃ khaga vṛkṣasya buddhvā karma svabhāvajam|
parityajyemam anyatra gaccha yatra sukhaṃ bhavet|| 118.41||
śuka uvāca|
na mūḍho 'asmi sureśāna māvamaṃsthā vaco mama|
śṛṇuṣva ca yathāprajñā mama deveśvara prabho|| 118.42||
acetano yathā hyagnirāpo vāyuśca tattvataḥ|
na tathā suraśārdūla vṛkṣagulmalatādayaḥ|| 118.43||
vihito hyeṣa saṃsāraḥ sarveṣām eva karmiṇām|
tasmādacetanatvaṃ te na vṛkṣeṣu sureśvara|| 118.44||
yathā ca buddhirvṛkṣāṇāṃ kathaṃ kuryāma sarvaśaḥ|
upakārāṃstu bhūtānām iti me tanniśāmaya|| 118.45||
svayambhuretānavadat sṛṣṭvā mukhyān mahāyaśāḥ|
prajānām upakārāya vartadhvam iti sarvaśaḥ|| 118.46||
tataste phalapuṣpatvakpravālādibhirantaśaḥ|
upakārāya vartante sarvabhūteṣu lokapa|| 118.47||
vāyuragnistathāpaśca kiṃ tavāviditaṃ prabho|
buddhipūrvaṃ pravartante yathāvaddhi nagāḥ śubhāḥ|| 118.48||
indra uvāca|
kathaṃ tavedaṃ vijñānaṃ ko dharmaḥ kaśca te śramaḥ|
etadveditum icchāmaḥ kathayasva khageśvara|| 118.49||
śuka uvāca|
janmaprabhṛti deveśa na mitradruhaṇe mama|
buddhiḥ samabhavannityaṃ mṛtyāvapi samāgate|| 118.50||
mātāpitṛparaścāhaṃ svadāraniratastathā|
nāvamanye ca bhūtāni ṛtukāle vrajāmi ca|| 118.51||
na bhakṣayāmi dhānyāni pareṣāṃ devatādhipa|
tena me jñānam amalaṃ pravṛttaṃ surasattama|| 118.52||
indra uvāca|
tuṣṭo 'asmi tava sadbuddhyā anayā khagasattama|
varaṃ vṛṇu pradāsyāmi yadbhavān manyate śubham|| 118.53||
śuka uvāca|
jīvatām eṣa devendra tvatprasādādvanaspatiḥ|
ato nānyam ahaṃ deva vṛṇuyāṃ varam uttamam|| 118.54||
indra uvāca|
karmaṇā svena jantūnāṃ gatayaḥ saṃprakīrtitāḥ|
svenaiva karmaṇā pātaḥ kiṃ tavānena buddhimat|| 118.55||
idaṃ vimānam āruhya mayā dattaṃ khagottama|
mama lokaṃ vraja kṣipraṃ stūyamāno yathā naraḥ|| 118.56||
śuka uvāca|
na lokānaham icchāmi na vimānaṃ na vai sukham|
prayācitaṃ prayacchasva jīvatām eṣa vai nagaḥ|| 118.57||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sadbhāvaṃ tasya taṃ jñātvā sarvaṃ ca surasattamaḥ|
cakāra sa yathāpūrvaṃ vṛkṣaṃ sarvaguṇānvitam|| 118.58||
śukaśca karmaṇā tena dṛḍhabhaktitayāpi ca|
dīneṣvabhyupapattyā ca brahmalokaṃ jagāma ha|| 118.59||
iti skandapurāṇe vāmantīrthayātrāyāmaṣṭādaśottaraśatatamo
.adhyāyaḥ|| 118.118||

skandapurana119
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste daivatāḥ sarve kṛmilāṃ nāma vai purīm|
upāgatā hyavaikṣanta tatra cedaṃ mahāmune|| 119.1||
brāhmaṇī gautamī nāma rudrāṇīva yathāparā|
dhārmikī ca vadānyā ca tapasā dagdhakilbiṣā|| 119.2||
tasyāstapasi saktāyā brahmalokaṃ gate patau|
kṛṣṇasarpeṇa mahatā suto daṣṭo mamāra ha|| 119.3||
taṃ deśam āgamat tatra vyādho 'arjunaka ityuta|
sa āgatastadāpaśyadviṣeṇa samabhiplutam|| 119.4||
sa gatvā gautamīṃ prāha suto 'ayaṃ te tapodhane|
daṣṭo 'ahinā mamārāśu kiṃ nainam avabudhyase|| 119.5||
sā tathoktā samāgamya putraṃ dṛṣṭvā gatāyuṣam|
ruroda bahudhā vyāsa mṛtāpatyā mahāvratā|| 119.6||
tasyā vilapamānāyā vyādhaḥ so 'arjunakastadā|
bilaṃ khanitvā niṣkṛṣya tam ahiṃ samabandhata|| 119.7||
sa baddhastena duṣṭātmā kṛṣṇasarpaḥ suduḥkhitaḥ|
uvāca taṃ tadā vyādhaṃ yo 'asāvarjunakaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 119.8||
kiṃ mayā tava baddhena nādharmaṃ paripaśyasi|
na caiva bhakṣyā martyānāṃ vayaṃ kiṃ māṃ na muñcasi|| 119.9||
arjuna uvāca|
tvām ādya khaṇḍaśaḥ kṛtvā bhakṣaṃ dāsyāmi barhiṇe|
tvayāyaṃ bhakṣito yasmādṛṣiputro mamāra ha|| 119.10||
sarpa uvāca|
kālena codito 'ahaṃ taṃ daṣṭavānṛṣiputrakam|
na māṃ doṣeṇārjunaka kṣeptum arhasi tattvataḥ|| 119.11||
arjuna uvāca|
codito yadi kālena daṣṭavānasi pannaga|
nimittaṃ tvaṃ hi maraṇe tasmāddhaṃsyāmi te bhṛśam|| 119.12||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sā gautamī vyāsa kālaṃ mṛtyum athākarot|
duḥkhena parameṇārtā kālo bhītastato 'abhyagāt|| 119.13||
kāla uvāca|
ahaṃ hi sarvasattvānāṃ kālo nāstyatra saṃśayaḥ|
codito mṛtyunaivāhaṃ hatavānṛṣiputrakam|| 119.14||
arjuna uvāca|
tvayā vā mṛtyunā vāyaṃ codito daṣṭavān yadi|
vadhe nimittam eṣo 'asya tasmādenaṃ nihanmyaham|| 119.15||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha mṛtyustadābhyetya taṃ deśaṃ sumahāmanāḥ|
gautamyāstapaso bhīta idaṃ provāca susvaram|| 119.16||
aham apyeṣa saṃbaddhaṃ niyatyā susamāhitaḥ|
mārayāmi na me doṣaṃ kartum arhasi suvrate|| 119.17||
arjuna uvāca|
niyatirvāstu mṛtyurvā kālo vāpyastu kāraṇam|
kṛṣṇasarpo nimittaṃ tu tasmādvadhyasrna saṃśayaḥ|| 119.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
athāgānniyatistatra uvācedaṃ ca sā tadā|
gautamīṃ duḥkhitāṃ vyāsa bhītā prāha tadā vacaḥ|| 119.19||
kṛtāntavaśagā sādhvi jantūn nityam atandritā|
pāśairbaddhvā vaśaṃ mṛtyornayāmi varavarṇinī|| 119.20||
kṛtānta uvāca|
ahaṃ hi kiṃkaraḥ sādhvi yamasya sumahātmanaḥ|
tena pracodito jantūn nayāmi yamasādanam|| 119.21||
arjuna uvāca|
yamo 'api vā kṛtānto vā ete vāpyasya kāraṇam|
naivam evaṃ durācāro vimokṣyeta kadācana|| 119.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato yamastadā vyāsa svayam eva mahāmanāḥ|
tatrāgāt tām idaṃ caiva gautamīṃ so 'abhyuvāca ha|| 119.23||
nāhaṃ naite mahāsattvāstava putrasya kāraṇam|
maraṇe tasya vīkṣasva śṛṇu cāpi vaco mama|| 119.24||
jantūnāṃ dehasaṃyogo dharmādharmakṛtaḥ śubhe|
viyogaścāpi dehena tābhyām eva kṣayāt punaḥ|| 119.25||
dehināṃ dharma evaika āyuṣo heturucyate|
tatkṣaye maranaṃ proktaṃ kālo mṛtyuśca sa smṛtaḥ|| 119.26||
kṛte varṣasahasraistu caturbhiḥ kāla ucyate|
tretāyāṃ tu trisāhasro dvāpare dvisahasrikaḥ|| 119.27||
kalau tu śatam evāhuḥ kālaṃ jantormahāvrate|
akāle 'anyat tataḥ proktaṃ taccāpi maraṇaṃ śṛṇu|| 119.28||
indriyeṣvasya ye devā vasanti dvipadāṃ vare|
te 'asya sarve harantyekaṃ bhāgaṃ daivatasattamāḥ|| 119.29||
cakṣuṣā paśyato duṣṭaṃ duṣṭaṃ ca bruvatastathā|
śṛṇvanto manvataścaiva budyataścāpi paśyataḥ|| 119.30||
tathā sparśayataścaiva jighrato bhuñjato 'api vā|
ādānādgamanāccaiva ānandotsargatastathā|| 119.31||
bhāgaṃ bhūtāni cānyaṃ tu haranti punareva hi|
suduṣṭaṃ vartatasteṣu bhāgaṃ ca vyādhayo 'aparam|| 119.32||
aparaṃ pitaro bhāgaṃ devāścānyam ato 'aparam|
aparaṃ carṣayo vahniścandrādityau grahāstathā|| 119.33||
tasyaivaṃ dehinaḥ sādhvi yāvadevāhṛtaṃ bhavet|
tāvadeva sa jīveta akālaḥ sa ca vakṣyate|| 119.34||
yathā ca mriyate janturakāle tapasaidhite|
tathā śṛṇu mamādyeha gadato varavarṇini|| 119.35||
yāvanna hīyate tasya jantorāyurmahāvrate|
tāvat sa jīvitaṃ prāpya tasyānte mriyate punaḥ|| 119.36||
tasya yenāparādhena āyurdevā haranti tat|
tenādharmo mahāṃstasya utpanno jīvitāntakaḥ|| 119.37||
prādurbhūtastadā sādhvi vyādhirmarmāṇi kṛntati|
sa kṛttamarmā hyavaśo dehaṃ tyaktvā mahāvrate|| 119.38||
anyaddehaṃ samāsādya gatim anyāṃ prapadyate|
ye 'asya vyādhiṃ na kurute so 'adharmo 'anugrahāt punaḥ|| 119.39||
devānāṃ dehavāsānāṃ tam apyanyena hanti vai|
viṣaśastraprapatanairjantubhiśca pṛthagvidhaiḥ|
anyaiśca bahubhirghorairnātra doṣaḥ prapaśyataḥ|| 119.40||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sā tapasā dṛṣṭvā gautamī sumahāvratā|
tam arjunakam āhedaṃ vacanaṃ duḥkhavarjitā|| 119.41||
gautamyuvāca|
muñcārjunaka nāyaṃ me pannago vadham arhati|
āviṣṭo 'ayam adharmeṇa daivataiścādaśat sutam|| 119.42||
īśvarāste mahātmāno jantūn āviśya cetanān|
acetanāṃśca sarve 'atra prayuñjanti yathātatham|| 119.43||
mṛta eṣa svadharmeṇa nāsti doṣastapasvinām|
gacchadhvaṃ daivatāḥ sarve svān gṛhān kim ihāsyate|| 119.44||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastā devatāḥ sarvāḥ preṣitā brahmayoṣitā|
samam ūcustadā vyāsa gautamīṃ tām idaṃ vacaḥ|| 119.45||
devā ūcuḥ|
tuṣṭāḥ sma tava dharmajñe tapasā dagdhakilbiṣe|
jīvatām eṣa te putraḥ svadharme cāvatiṣṭhatu|| 119.46||
sarpa eṣa svayaṃ sādhvi adharmo mūrtimān sthitaḥ|
vyadharūpī ca dharmo 'ayaṃ paśyaitau sumahāvrate|| 119.47||
parīkṣā te kṛtā hyeṣā devairetairmahāvrate|
tavākṣayā bhaviṣyanti lokāḥ sarve na saṃśayaḥ|| 119.48||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste sahasā tatra devā indrapurogamāḥ|
avaikṣanta yathāvṛttaṃ tacca sarvaṃ nyavedayam|| 119.49||
snātvā cānyadagacchante punastīrthaṃ samāhitāḥ|
sarva eva mahābhāgāstathānyāni punaḥ punaḥ|| 119.50||
krameṇa viharantaste kṛtyām abhyāgamat punaḥ|
yatra kṛtyā hatā purvaṃ devendreṇa mahaujasā|| 119.51||
vyāsa uvāca|
kena sotpāditā kṛtyā kimarthaṃ kasya vā vibho|
kathaṃ ca nihatā bhūya etadicchāmi veditum|| 119.52||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tṛṇabinduriti khyāta āsīdrājā mahābalaḥ|
sa provāca munīn sapta idaṃ vacanakovidaḥ|| 119.53||
yājayadhvaṃ hi māṃ viprā dāsye vittaṃ hi vo bahu|
te 'abruvan na vayaṃ sādho yājayāma nareśvara|| 119.54||
sa dīkṣito yadānyena anāvṛṣṭyā mahāmanāḥ|
te vai bubhukṣayāviṣṭā yajñaṃ prāptā yadṛcchayā|| 119.55||
atha tānabravīdrājā brūta kiṃ pradadāni vaḥ|
ūcuste kruddhavacanāḥ sutaṃ no datsva pārthiva|| 119.56||
tebhyaḥ satkṛtya putraṃ ca dhanaṃ caiva sa pārthivaḥ|
praṇamya bahumānena pārāśaryopapādayat|| 119.57||
tathā tasyānatasyaivaṃ dravyaṃ hitvā tapodhanāḥ|
sutaṃ gṛhītvāgacchante saukumāryāt sa bālakaḥ|| 119.58||
kṣuttṛṣābhyarditastatra adhvanā ca mamāra ha|
dāvāgnau te ca taṃ nyasya nirīkṣanto 'avatasthire|| 119.59||
teṣāṃ tatrekṣatāṃ vyāsa ājagāma narādhipaḥ|
uvāca tānṛṣīṃścedaṃ prahasan divyakuṇḍalaḥ|| 119.60||
tṛṇabinduruvāca|
yūyaṃ pratigrahaṃ matto nāgṛhṇata tapodhanāḥ|
yājayadhvaṃ na caivāsmānmunayastapasaidhitāḥ|| 119.61||
iha doṣaṃ na paśyadhvaṃ maraṇe 'asya śiśordvijāḥ|
adharmye cāyaśasye ca aho 'adharme hi vo matiḥ|| 119.62||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste tam anādṛtya anuktvā kiṃcideva ca|
jagmuranyāṃ diśaṃ vyāsa vane kṣutparipīḍitāḥ|| 119.63||
tṛṇabinduśca tapasā tatra vṛkṣān bahūṃstadā|
asṛjat tatkṣaṇādvyāsa teṣāṃ sukhahitepsayā|| 119.64||
te ca tadvanam āsādya bahūn vṛkṣān phalānvitān|
apaśyanta tadā vyāsa parāṃ tuṣṭiṃ ca te yayuḥ|| 119.65||
gṛhītvā bibhiduścaiva dadṛśuścaiva teṣvatha|
suvarṇam annaṃ bhakṣāṃśca tathā raupyaṃ ca suprabham|| 119.66||
tṛṇabindukṛtaṃ tacca te 'amanyanta taponvitāḥ|
tataste tadvanaṃ tyaktvā ṛṣayaḥ sapta suvratāḥ|
anyāṃ diśaṃ prapadyanta tṛṇabinduścukopa ca|| 119.67||
uvāca tānṛṣīn gatvā praṇataḥ prāñjaliśca saḥ|
manyunātiparītātmā saṃvigno 'atha narādhipaḥ|| 119.68||
tṛṇabinduruvāca|
naivāsmi patito viprā duṣṭakarmā na caiva ha|
na caiva varjito viprairna cāyajvā na pāpakṛt|| 119.69||
narādhipānāṃ vaṃśe 'asmi jātaḥ śuddhe tapodhanāḥ|
samyak prajāḥ pālayāmi kiṃ māṃ na bahu manyata|| 119.70||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā ṛṣayaste mahāvratāḥ|
ūcurna te vayaṃ rājan pratigṛhṇīma sarvathā|| 119.71||
śobhano 'asi guṇairyuktaḥ prajāpālaḥ prajāpatiḥ|
saṃtuṣṭāḥ smo na te dravyaṃ pratigṛhṇīma bhūpate|| 119.72||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktvā rājānaṃ sarva eva yayurmune|
so 'api rājā mahāmanyustadā dīptaṃ hutāśanam|| 119.73||
juhāva kṛtyāṃ tasmācca cakāra sumahābalām|
yātudhānīm iti khyātām uvācedaṃ ca tāṃ tadā|| 119.74||
gatvā sapta munīn kṛtye bhakṣayasva mahābale|
upadhārya hi nāmāni vasiṣṭhādīṃstapodhanān|| 119.75||
sā gatvā tu śubhān nāma divyāṃ puṣkariṇīṃ śubhām|
tasyāstīraṃ samāsādya tasthau tān vai pratīkṣatī|| 119.76||
ṛṣayaste 'api saṃvignāḥ kṣuttṛṣṇāvyākulendriyāḥ|
anyān deśān vimārgantaḥ śubhāṃ vāpīṃ yayustataḥ|| 119.77||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tadgamane vyāsa dṛṣṭvā doṣaṃ puraṃdara|
parivrājakaveṣeṇa śvadvitīyo 'abhyagacchata|| 119.78||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā te 'abruvan sarve parasparam anulbaṇam|
hasantaṃ taṃ mahābāhuṃ tridaṇḍavyagrapāṇinam|| 119.79||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ|
nūnam eṣa divārātrau nityam eva hyatandritaḥ|
cakhāda yata eṣo 'atra tato 'ayaṃ pīvaro 'abhavat|| 119.80||
athavottānahasto 'ayaṃ nityam eva prayācakaḥ|
tapaḥsvādhyāyavikretā tenāyaṃ pīvaro 'abhavat|| 119.81||
tam evaṃ bahudhā kalpya ṛṣayaste tapodhanāḥ|
papracchuramitātmānaṃ kastvam ityeva vādinaḥ|| 119.82||
indra uvāca|
ahaṃ parivrāḍviprendrā āgacchāmi daśerakāt|
prayāsyāmi śubhāṃ vāpīṃ nāmnāhaṃ tu śunassakhā|| 119.83||
śvāno mama sadā hīṣṭāḥ śunāṃ caiva sadā hyaham|
tasmācchunaḥsakhā nāmnā khyāto 'ahaṃ dvijasattamāḥ|| 119.84||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste saha tenaiva śubhāṃ puṣkariṇīṃ yayuḥ|
dadṛśustāṃ ca kṛtyāṃ te tayā caiva nivāritāḥ|| 119.85||
yadi vā rocate viprā asyām abhyavagāhitum|
nāmāni kathayitveha caradhvaṃ sukham avyayāḥ|| 119.86||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste tāṃ tadā kanyām ūcurevaṃ bhavatviti|
śvasakhā cedam āhainānṛṣīn sarvānariṃdamaḥ|| 119.87||
viprā iyaṃ yātudhānī neyaṃ prakṛtamānuṣī|
bhavitavyaṃ hi kāryeṇa yatheyaṃ vadate hi vaḥ|| 119.88||
te yūyaṃ yadi manyadhvaṃ śreyaḥ paramakaṃ hitam|
tathā nāmāni vibrūta yatheyaṃ nopadhārayet|| 119.89||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ bhavatviti procya te vyāsa munayaḥ śubhāḥ|
nāmāni tasyāḥ śrāvyaiva yatheṣṭaṃ te jagāhire|| 119.90||
nairuktāni svanāmāni durbodhāni ca te 'abruvan|
na mene yāni kṛtyā sā tataste jalam āviśan|| 119.91||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣām alakṣayitvā sā nāmāni tu śikhodbhavā|
śvasakhaṃ prāha brūhi tvaṃ tato yāsyasi vā na vā|| 119.92||
śvasakha uvāca|
śunām asmi sakhā krūre śvabhiśca saha saṃgataḥ|
śvasakhaṃ tena māṃ viddhi yātudhāni niśācari|| 119.93||
yātudhānyuvāca|
sakṛdeva punarbrūhi nāma tvaṃ mānuṣādhama|
tato yāsyasi viprāṇāṃ samīpaṃ vidito mama|| 119.94||
śvasakha uvāca|
śunām asmi sakhā devaḥ sakhyaṃ me 'anapagaṃ śvabhiḥ|
śvasakhā tena hanmi tvā yātudhāni niśāmaya|| 119.95||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktvā tāṃ krūrāṃ tridaṇḍena sureśvaraḥ|
mūrdhni ājaghāna tenāśu bhasmasādabhavacca sā|| 119.96||
tṛṇabindusutaścāsau kṛtyayā hatamātrayā|
śakreṇa jīvitastūrṇaṃ pitaraṃ samupāgamat|| 119.97||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ tāṃ sa nihatyendraḥ śvasakhā śaktinandana|
mṛṇālabisapadmāni ṛṣīṇām aharat punaḥ|| 119.98||
tataste samyaguttīrṇā apaśyanto ruṣānvitāḥ|
cakrire śapathān viprāḥ parasparam anuvratāḥ|| 119.99||
tataste sarva evaitya śvasakhaṃ munisattamāḥ|
abruvaṃstvayi śaṅkā no brūhi yena vimucyase|| 119.100||
śvasakha uvāca|
yo vo harati mūlāni puṣpāṇi ca phalāni ca|
sa sukhī miṣṭam aśnātu sasuhṛt saparigrahaḥ|| 119.101||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste ṛṣayo vyāsa ūcuḥ sarve puraṃdaram|
tvayā gṛhītaṃ dravyaṃ nastat prayacchasva naḥ punaḥ|| 119.102||
teṣāṃ sa bhagavān vyāsa mūlāni ca phalāni ca|
sarvāṇyevādadat prīta idaṃ covāca tānṛṣīn|| 119.103||
indra uvāca|
iyaṃ kṛtyā hatā viprā yuṣmadarthe purā kṛtā|
mayā hitārthaṃ yuṣmākaṃ tridaṇḍena tapodhanāḥ|
kruddhena rājñā yuṣmākaṃ kṛtaiṣā tṛṇabindunā|| 119.104||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tām āgamya tato devā ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
viṣṇuṃ taṃ snapayāṃ cakrustīrthe ṛṣigaṇārcite|| 119.105||
tataste himavacchailaṃ samāgamya madānvitāḥ|
ayājayaṃstadā viṣṇum aśvamedhena suvratāḥ|| 119.106||
tasmin yajati deveśastryambakaḥ sagaṇeśvaraḥ|
yajñaṃ prati mudā yukta ājagāma vihāyasā|| 119.107||
vyāsa uvāca|
aho vata tvayedaṃ me kathitaṃ brahmaṇaḥ suta|
yātudhānyā upākhyānaṃ paraṃ guhyaṃ sudurvidam|| 119.108||
idaṃ hi guhyaṃ paramaṃ mahārthavat sadā yaśasyaṃ paramaṃ ca pāvanam|
tvayā mahāyoga yathāvadīritaṃ purāmṛtaṃ pūrṇaśaśiprabhaṃ yathā|| 119.109||
iti skandapurāṇe vāmanatīrthayātrāyāṃ
yātudhānyupākhyāne ūnaviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 119.119||

skandapurana120
vyāsa uvāca|
ataḥ paraṃ sa bhagavān yathāgāt parameśvaraḥ|
yajñena yajamānaṃ taṃ samīkṣya kathayasva naḥ|| 120.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa tu śūladharo devo bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyām uvācedaṃ devīṃ himavataḥ sutām|| 120.2||
devyadya subhage loke kṛṣṇapakṣāṣṭamī śubhā|
rajanyām adya yāsyāva śmaśānānyabhivīkṣitum|| 120.3||
devyuvāca|
yathā te rocate deva tathā bhavatu lokapa|
taveṣṭaṃ yanmahādeva mamāpi dviguṇaṃ hi tat|| 120.4||
atha tasmin dine vyāsa ujjayinyāṃ mahāmune|
brāhmaṇasya suto bālaḥ śucirvidvān mamāra ha|| 120.5||
taṃ te 'abhisaṃskṛtya tadā alaṃkṛtya yathāvidhi|
krośantaśca rudantaśca śmaśānāyaiva ninyire|| 120.6||
te śmaśānaṃ tadā nītvā bālaṃ taṃ raktapādakam|
snehādduḥkhaparītāśca rurudurbahudhā bhṛśam|| 120.7||
tathā tān rudato vīkṣya kruddho gṛdhraḥ kṣudhānvitaḥ|
prājñavat sa tu saṃdiśya tānuvāca dvijāṃstadā|| 120.8||
viprāḥ śṛṇuta me vākyaṃ mānuṣā yadvadāmi vaḥ|
buddhihīnāḥ stha suvyaktaṃ niśām ayata madvacaḥ|| 120.9||
mṛta eṣa hi kālena kiṃ śocatha yathābudhāḥ|
rudito naiṣa jīveta svārthaṃ kuruta vijvarāḥ|| 120.10||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā tadā tyaktvā sutaṃ yayuḥ|
muhurmuhurnirīkṣanta atha tān jambuko 'abravīt|| 120.11||
aho dhiṅmānuṣāḥ sarve vīkṣadhvaṃ buddhivarjitāḥ|
niḥsnehāścākṛtajñāśca tyaktvainaṃ yātha vai katham|| 120.12||
duḥkhena labhyate putrastathā caiva prasūyate|
duḥkhena ca punaḥ krūrā varddhate vyādhyupadrutaḥ|| 120.13||
vismṛtāni hi vastāni cāṭūni subahūni vai|
akarodyānyayaṃ bālo 'aho niḥsnehatā hi vaḥ|| 120.14||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste jambukavacaḥ śrutvā vyāsa samāgatāḥ|
parivārya rudantaśca tasthuḥ pitṛvane tadā|| 120.15||
athāgānniśi deveśaḥ kapardī priyayā saha|
gaṇaiḥ sarvairvṛto devaḥ saha nandīśvareṇa ca|| 120.16||
sa tān īśaḥ samabhyetya sarvabhūtasukhāvahaḥ|
varado 'asmīti tāṃstatra rudataḥ pratyuvāca ha|| 120.17||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste dīnayā vācā bāṣpaparyākulekṣaṇāḥ|
ūcurjīvaḥ suto nāyaṃ bhaveddevājñayā tava|| 120.18||
teṣāṃ sa bhagavāṃstatra jīvayitvā sutaṃ śiśum|
gaṇeśatvaṃ dadau nityaṃ vāsaṃ tatraiva cākṣayam|| 120.19||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa tāṃ niśāṃ prāpya śmaśānāni yathāvidhi|
gatvā jagāma vaidūryaṃ kūṭaṃ himavataḥ śubham|| 120.20||
sa dīptatejā vibhuravyayātmā pinākadhṛk parvatakūṭavāsī|
uvāca tān yajñavareṇa dīkṣitān varaṃ vṛṇīdhvaṃ tridivaikasaṃśrayāḥ|| 120.21||
iti skandapurāṇe viṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 120.120||

skandapurana121
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te 'atha dṛṣṭvā mahādevaṃ saptalokaikabāndhavam|
ūcuḥ prāñjalayaḥ sarve jānubhyāṃ śirasā natāḥ|| 121.1||
bhagava/llokakāmena hariṇā devasattama|
kṛtaḥ pratigrahaḥ pūrvaṃ yena pāpmā tam arcchata|| 121.2||
tadasya jagato nātha bhaktasya praṇatasya ca|
asmābhiryācyamānastvaṃ kuru śreyaḥ sureśvaraḥ|| 121.3||
samāpyatām ayaṃ yajñaḥ pāpmanā mucyatāṃ hariḥ|
svām ūrjāṃ pratipadyantāṃ devāḥ sarve savāsavāḥ|| 121.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bhagavān hṛṣitānanaḥ|
samāpya yajñaṃ śūlena giriṃ taṃ samadārayat|| 121.5||
tasmādbhedāt tato hi āpaḥ sudhāśaṅkhendupāṇḍarāḥ|
niḥsṛtāstatra te viṣṇuṃ snapayāṃ cakrire tadā|| 121.6||
tasyātha snātamātrasya śarīrādabhiniḥsṛtā|
pāpmāsurī mahāghorā vikṛtā vikṛtānanā|| 121.7||
devānabhidrutā hantuṃ niruddhā devabandhunā|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
uvāca tāṃ na hantavyā devāḥ sarve savāsavāḥ|| 121.8||
ihaiva ca tava sthānaṃ bhaviṣyati supūjitam|
puṇyā ca sarvatīrthebhyaḥ sarvapātakanāśanī|| 121.9||
sapta pūrvān parāṃścaiva tārayiṣyasi nityaśaḥ|
saṃdhyeti jagati khyātā sarvatīrthavarā śubhā|| 121.10||
vāridhārā śubhā divyā sarvayajñaphalapradā|
tvām upāsya kulān sapta tārayiṣyanti mānavāḥ|| 121.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste daivatāḥ sarve rudrasya vacanāt tadā|
arcayitvā yathānyāyaṃ devadevam umāpatim|| 121.12||
devasyāyatanaṃ kṛtvā jagmustridivam eva ca|
gateṣu devasaṃgheṣu śivakūṭe tadā hariḥ|| 121.13||
aśvamedhaṃ tadā yaṣṭvā devam ārādhayat sthitaḥ|
tasyātha varṣaiḥ ṣaḍbhistu sahasreṇa ca tanyataḥ|
māsaiḥ ṣaḍbhiśca deveśastutoṣa vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 121.14||
somaḥ sanandiḥ sagaṇa idaṃ provāca taṃ punaḥ|
hṛṣyamāṇaḥ sutuṣṭātmā brūhi kiṃ pradadāni te|| 121.15||
viṣṇuruvāca|
bhagavan pāpmanā vāpi tapasā vāpi lokapa|
lopo na me yathā syādvai tanmamācakṣva kālahan|| 121.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ prahasya deveśaḥ prīyamāṇaḥ prajāpatiḥ|
uvāca viṣṇum āmantrya guhyaṃ cara mahāvratam|| 121.17||
sa cātha kṛtarakṣastaṃ sarvadharmāvahaṃ śubham|
yogaṃ yantraṃ vrataṃ caiva paramaiśvaryasādhanam|| 121.18||
yat tat pāśupataṃ divyaṃ vidhānaṃ sārvakāmikam|
taccīrtvā dvādaśa samāḥ paramaiśvaryam āptavān|| 121.19||
tasya devaḥ svayaṃ śūlī tuṣṭaḥ prekṣya tathāvidham|
śarīrārdhaṃ dadau tasmai tadabhūdviṣṇuśaṃkaram|| 121.20||
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyānmartyaḥ sadā parvasu parvasu|
arcayecchivaviṣṇuṃ ca sa gacchet paramāṃ gatim|| 121.21||
evaṃ sa viṣṇurjitvā tu vāmanaḥ sumahābalaḥ|
trailokyaṃ sarvadevebhyaḥ sarvaṃ prati samarpayat|| 121.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato devaiḥ samākrānte trailokye munipuṃgava|
ye 'asurā hataśeṣāstu te samāśritya dānavau|| 121.23||
tārakaṃ ca mayaṃ caiva cakruryuddhaṃ sahāmaraiḥ|
mayaśca tārakaścaiva putrapautrasamāvṛtau|| 121.24||
vipracittiśca danujo ye ca tasya sutāḥ smṛtāḥ|
nivātakavacāḥ sarve paulomāḥ kālakāsutāḥ|
saiṃhikeyāśca vikrāntā bāleyaśca tathā gaṇaḥ|| 121.25||
ete cānye ca bahavo dānavā baladarpitāḥ|
saṃnaddhāḥ samabhikruddhā āhvayanta tadā surān|| 121.26||
saṃprekṣya tān āhvayato devā api sudaṃśitāḥ|
taiḥ sahaitya tadā cakruḥ samaraṃ samaraiṣiṇaḥ|| 121.27||
teṣāṃ tadabhavadyuddhaṃ tumulaṃ lomaharṣaṇam|
varṣāṇāṃ tu śatānyaṣṭau sahasrāṇi ca ṣoḍaśa|| 121.28||
divyāni na ca saṃgrāme ekapakṣe jayo 'abhavat|
atha devāstadā yuddhe saiṃhikeyairdurāsadaiḥ|| 121.29||
parājitā mahāsattvāḥ siṃhaiḥ paśugaṇā iva|
teṣāṃ tadbalam ālakṣya sahasrākṣaḥ puraṃdaraḥ|| 121.30||
jagāma devadeveśam śaraṇaṃ rudram avyayam|
sa gatvā svarṇacūḍasya gireḥ śṛṅge kṛtālayam|| 121.31||
devyā saha mahādevam apaśyadgaṇasaṃvṛtam|
dīpyamānaṃ yathā vahniṃ durdṛśyam akṛtātmabhiḥ|| 121.32||
tam asau nandinā pūrvam ākhyāto devasattamaḥ|
dṛṣṭvā praṇamya śirasā idaṃ vacanam ūcivān|| 121.33||
deva varṣaśatānyaṣṭau sahasrāṇi ca ṣoḍaśa|
divyāni samatītāni saṃgrāmasya divaukasām|| 121.34||
tārakaśca mayaścaiva dānavau yuddhadurmadau|
tau āśrityāsurāḥ sarve devān ghnanti yathā paśūn|| 121.35||
teṣāṃ tu vadhyamānānāṃ devānāṃ devasattama|
jīvitaṃ saṃprayacchasva yathā vā deva yujyate|| 121.36||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|
cintayitvā tatastatra rāma rāmetyathābravīt|| 121.37||
bhagavānuvāca|
rāma rāma mahābāho cīrṇaṃ te sumahat tapaḥ|
gaccha devān suyuddhena kuru sarvān gatajvarān|| 121.38||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktastadā rāmo jāmadagnyaḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca dīnayā vācā praṇamya bahumānataḥ|| 121.39||
rāma uvāca|
bhagavannalpavīryo 'asmi tapasā karṣito bhṛśam|
anastravicca deveśa na śakṣye saṃyugaṃ vibho|| 121.40||
devavava uvāca|
gaccha śakṣyasi viprādya yoddhuṃ tvaṃ tvadya mā śucaḥ|
ahaṃ tvāpyāyayiṣyāmi mā vyathāṃ kuru bhārgava|| 121.41||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhagavānindraṃ prāha devapatiṃ haraḥ|
eṣa haṃsyati te śatrūn ratham asmai prayaccha ca|| 121.42||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ praṇamya śakro 'api rāmam ādāya caiva ha|
jagāma taṃ tadoddeśaṃ saṃgrāmo yatra so 'abhavat|| 121.43||
tataḥ sa rathamukhyena saṃpādya tu puraṃdaraḥ|
rāmam āha svayaṃ śakraḥ saiṃhikeyānupāhvaya|| 121.44||
sa tena rathamukhyena rāmaḥ praharatāṃ varaḥ|
kavacī baddhatūṇīraḥ śarī khaḍgī śarāsanī|| 121.45||
baddhagodhā"gulitraśca baddhadhvajapatākavān|
abhidudrāva vegena saiṃhikeyān durāsadān|| 121.46||
teṣāṃ tasya ca saṃgrāmaḥ sughoraḥ samapadyata|
śārdūlānāṃ yathāraṇye siṃhena saha bhīṣaṇaḥ|| 121.47||
tatrādbhutam apaśyanta siddhagandharvacāraṇāḥ|
yedekopi tadā raṅge dṛśyate 'anekarūpavān|| 121.48||
nādadānaḥ śarāṃścitrān saṃdadhānastathaiva ca|
dhanurvikarṣamāṇo vā dṛśyate bhārgavastadā|| 121.49||
maṇḍalīkṛtam evāsya kārmukaṃ sumahat tadā|
dṛśyate śatrubhiścaiva durnirīkṣyaśca so 'abhavat|| 121.50||
teṣāṃ sa bhārgavaḥ kruddhaḥ parāvṛtya mahābalaḥ|
cikṣepaikaikaśo vyāsa mukhe tīkṣṇāñcharān daśa|| 121.51||
tatrādbhutam apaśyanta lāghavaṃ tasya dhīmataḥ|
sādhu sādhviti bhūtānāṃ tatra śabdo mahānabhūt|| 121.52||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
taiḥ śarairbhinnavadanāḥ saiṃhikeyā mahābalāḥ|
sagandhā nipatantyurvyāṃ tālā vāyvāhatā iva|| 121.53||
sa tadā daśasāhasrasteṣāṃ vai devavidviṣām|
bhārgaveṇa gaṇo dagdhaḥ kāleneva yathā jagat|| 121.54||
tato devāḥ saṛṣayo gandharvāśca sacāraṇāḥ|
sādhu sādhviti taṃ procya tuṣṭuvurhṛṣitānanāḥ|| 121.55||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tat karma saṃvīkṣya bhagavān pākaśāsanaḥ|
bahumānena saṃpūjya bhārgavaṃ saha daivataiḥ|| 121.56||
idam āha mahātejāḥ pariṣvajya punaḥ punaḥ|
tavaitat karma nānyasya sadṛśaṃ divi vidyate|| 121.57||
yadi te siṃhikāputrāḥ sahasaiva hatāstvayā|
tava vaitanmahat karma tripure tryambakasya vā|
na tvayāsti samo loke satyam etadbravīmyaham|| 121.58||
ete na tulyā devena mānuṣeṇa na kenacit|
avadhyāḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ tvayaikena niṣūditāḥ|| 121.59||
tasmāt tava vayaṃ tuṣṭāḥ prayacchāmo hyavadhyatām|
akṣayaṃ ca balaṃ yuddhe yaśaṃ ca paramaṃ bhuvi|| 121.60||
tryambakaśca varairdivyairiṣṭaistvāṃ pratipatsyate|
yathākāmaṃ ca yuddheṣu samūhaṃ tvaṃ vijeṣyasi|| 121.61||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam uktastairvyāsa devaistuṣṭairmahātapāḥ|
jagāma tryambakaṃ devaṃ hṛṣṭatuṣṭamanā yatiḥ|| 121.62||
devā api susaṃyattāstārakaṃ yuddhadurmadam|
avākiranta vegena mayena sahitaṃ tadā|| 121.63||
te daityavegapratiruddhavegā mahābalāḥ sindhusamānavegāḥ|
jaghnurbhṛśaṃ daityagaṇān nipatya siṃhā yathāraṇyacarā mataṅgān|| 121.64||
iti skandapurāṇe jāmadagnyavarapradāno nāma
ekaviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 121.121||

skandapurana122
sanatkumāra uvāca|
saiṃhikeyavadhaṃ dṛṣṭvā surāṇāṃ ca jayaṃ tathā|
sahasā daityasainyāni prabhagnāni samantataḥ|| 122.1||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
anyena pracyutastāro mayo vīro virocanaḥ|| 122.2||
vipracittiśca ṣaṇḍaśca prahlādaśca mahāsuraḥ|
kālanemistataḥ kruddhaḥ keśavaṃ prati saṃyuge|| 122.3||
sarathaṃ mahadāsthāya śatanalvordhvaketumat|
abhidudrāva vegena keśavaṃ prati dānavaḥ|| 122.4||
tasyāpatata evātha cakram apratighaṃ mahat|
sasarja keśavo vyāsa sa tadvyaṣṭambhayat tadā|| 122.5||
tadviṣṭabdhaṃ tadālakṣya sarve devāḥ pramanyavaḥ|
parājitā babhūvurhi viśastrāḥ kālaneminā|| 122.6||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
sa tān vidrāvya daityendro vimukhān pracakāra ha|
kṛtvā cakāra ca tadā lokapālatvam avyayaḥ|| 122.7||
bhuvaṃ dyāṃ ca tadā vyāpya vartamāno mahābalaḥ|
svayambhūriva lokāṃstrīnacarallokamāyayā|| 122.8||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
taṃ tathāvasthitaṃ dṛṣṭvā daityaṃ devāḥ savāsavāḥ|
bhayatrastāstadā jagmuḥ śaraṇaṃ harim avyayam|| 122.9||
śaraṇyaḥ sa ca deveśo haristryailokyabāndhavaḥ|
teṣāṃ prādādbhayatrāṇaṃ dānavasya vadhepsayā|| 122.10||
sa tadā dyāṃ bhuvaṃ caiva vyāpya rūpeṇa sarvaśaḥ|
cakraṃ tadabjaṃ sasmāra yat tadrudreṇa nirmitam|| 122.11||
tatastena tadā vyāsa dānavasya śiro mahat|
jahāra pakvaṃ tālāgrāt phalaṃ vāyurivoddhataḥ|| 122.12||
tasmin vinihate daitye tārakaśca mayaśca ha|
vinivṛttau mahāyodhau pātālaṃ prativegitau|| 122.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ vyāsābhavadyuddham ugraṃ tat tārakāmayam|
kālanemirhato yatra viśrutaśca virocanaḥ|| 122.14||
saiṃhikeyāśca vikrāntāstuhuṇḍaśca mahāsuraḥ|
surocanaḥ satāvarto hālo gārgyaśirāstathā|| 122.15||
vipākaḥ saha pākena caṇḍaḥ kārtasvanaḥ kubhaḥ|
ete cānye ca daityendrā nihatāstārakāmaye|
dhvaje punarhataḥ krūro vipracittiḥ sahānujaḥ|| 122.16||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ tadabhavadyuddhaṃ devānām asuraiḥ saha|
kathaṃ ca dhvaja ityevaṃ tasya nāma babhūva ha|| 122.17||
jāmadagnyaśca tat karma kṛtvā bhṛgukulodvahaḥ|
duṣkaraṃ sarvabhūtānām āgatastryambakāntikam|
kim ukto devadevena etadicchāmi veditum|| 122.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
jamadagnestadā sūnuramaraiḥ preṣitaḥ svayam|
jagāma guhyaṃ devasya puriścandraṃ niveśanam|| 122.19||
vyāsa uvāca|
kathaṃ tadabhavaddivyaṃ puriścandraṃ niveśanam|
sthānaṃ guhyaṃ maheśasya kathayasva dṛḍhavrata|| 122.20||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atra te saṃpravakṣyāmi durāvṛttaṃ mahāmate|
yacchrutvā pāpakarmāpi gaccheta paramāṃ gatim|| 122.21||
purābhūtāṃ mahātmānau naranārāyaṇāvṛṣī|
tābhyāṃ kāryeṇa devānāṃ brahmavadhyā kṛtā kila|| 122.22||
tayābhibhūtau tau devau pāpmayātimahābalau|
abhūtān naṣṭasaṃjñau tau tiryagyonigatau bhṛśam|| 122.23||
atha saṃvatsare divye samatīte 'amitātmavān|
āgādbrahmā svayaṃ tatra daivatairṛṣibhiḥ saha|| 122.24||
sa taṃ saṃbodhayāmāsa sanaraṃ devapastadā|
tathāpi hi na tau buddhau karmaṇā saṃvṛtau bhṛśam|| 122.25||
tān brahmā sa tadā prāha sarvāneva divaukasaḥ|
yūyaṃ nārāyaṇasyārthe caradhvaṃ dharmam uttamam|| 122.26||
tato vimokṣyate devaḥ sanaro brahmavadhyayā|
tam evaṃvādinaṃ devāḥ praṇamya śirasā tadā|
ūcuḥ prāñjalayaḥ sarve kiṃ tapaḥ karma śādhi naḥ|| 122.27||
brahmovāca|
japadhvaṃ prayatāḥ sarve vāyubhakṣā jitendriyāḥ|
rudrāṇāṃ hṛdayaṃ samyak tato yogam avāpsyatha|| 122.28||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam astviti procya jajapuḥ salileśayāḥ|
ṛṣibhiḥ saha deveśā varṣāyutaśatāni ṣaṭ|| 122.29||
atha kālena mahatā teṣāṃ yuktātmanāṃ tadā|
yogaḥ prādurabhūt sūkṣmo yato 'agnirabhavacchubhaḥ|| 122.30||
tenāgninā brahmavadhyā naranārāyaṇau tadā|
sā dagdhā saṃparityajya udakaṃ praviveśa ha|| 122.31||
nāstayāpaḥ samāviṣṭā rasavatyo na jajñire|
agandhāśca vivarṇāśca prabhāvatyo na caiva ha|
pṛthivī cālpavīryābhūt tejastigmaṃ ca nābhavat|| 122.32||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste taṃ tathā dṛṣṭvā yuyujurbhūya eva ca|
hṛdayaṃ jajapuścaiva rudrāṇāṃ yuktamānasāḥ|| 122.33||
athāgādbhagavān devaḥ śūlapāṇirvṛṣadhvajaḥ|
uvāca devāṃstuṣṭo 'asmi brūta yadvo 'abhikāṅkṣitam|| 122.34||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastā devatāḥ samyagrudraṃ dṛṣṭvābhiremire|
tuṣṭuvuścānatā bhūtvā yajñajīmūtavāhanam|| 122.35||
devā ūcuḥ|
namaḥ paramadevāya yugāntānalavarcase|
salile tapyamānāya rudrāṇāṃ hṛdayāya ca|| 122.36||
mahāparaśuhastāya hiraṇyāyatanāya ca|
vasūnāṃ pataye caiva devānāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 122.37||
śucaye rerihāṇāya sadyojātāya manyave|
grahāṇāṃ pataye caiva grahāṇāṃ hṛdayāya ca|| 122.38||
mahāgrahānuyātāya graharājāya vai namaḥ|
namaḥ śamadamogrāya ugradaṇḍadharāya ca|| 122.39||
yamāya yamanāthāya yamadaṇḍadharāya ca|
namaḥ paramadevāya parāṇāṃ paramāya ca|| 122.40||
mahatāṃ pataye caiva kamaṇḍaludharāya ca|
vāmadevāya jyeṣṭhāya paśūnāṃ pataye namaḥ|| 122.41||
pradhānapataye caiva pradhānasya pravartine|
namaḥ sahasravaktrāya gadine śūline namaḥ|| 122.42||
namaḥ pavanarūpāya bahurūpāya vedhase|
namaḥ kratuvihantre ca kāmānalavighātine|| 122.43||
namaśchandoṅgarūpāya virūpanayanāya ca|
indriyagrāmaghātāya namo vedāntagāya ca|| 122.44||
namo 'astvaśanighātāya manasām unmanāya ca|
vedavedāṅgamālāya namaste padmamāline|| 122.45||
namaḥ śailapradāhāya śailajātodbhavāya ca|
mahate viśvarūpāya mahadbhirmahitāya ca|| 122.46||
sahasraśatanetrāya lalāṭanayanāya ca|
mahāyogapraṇetre ca tathā tatpuruṣāya ca|| 122.47||
namo vedarahasyāya devavedastutāya ca|
yogine dhyāyamānāya aśanīpātahāsine|| 122.48||
hṛcchayāya namaste 'astu namaḥ sarvagatāya ca|
kumāravaranāthāya kumārajanakāya ca|| 122.49||
daṇḍahastāya carate antakāyājitāya ca|
śubhāya śubharūpāya śubhasarvapravartine|| 122.50||
śivāya śubharūpāya sadā sarvaviśāya ca|
dhanurvedarahasyāya dhanurvedapravartine|| 122.51||
sarvapāpāpahantre ca sarvapāpmavighātine|
śivaḥ saumyaśca deveśa diśa no yanmanogatam|| 122.52||
yadapavyāhṛtaṃ kiṃcidasmābhirbhagavan vibho|
tat sarvaṃ bhaktavātsalyādasmākaṃ kṣantum arhasi|| 122.53||
pāpmayābhiparītātmā devabandhurayaṃ vibho|
nareṇa saha deveśa sa bhaveccandranirmalaḥ|| 122.54||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ya imaṃ tryambakastotraṃ bhaktimān satataṃ naraḥ|
paṭhati prayato vyāsa pāpmayā sa vimucyate|| 122.55||
sarvapāpaiśca mucyeta naṣṭaṃ ca labhate punaḥ|
na ca durgatim āpnoti yadi syādvai supāpakṛt|| 122.56||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa bhagavān devaiḥ stutastuṣṭaśca lokapaḥ|
uvāca devān deveśaḥ sarvān satyavatīsuta|| 122.57||
devadeva uvāca|
bho devāḥ parituṣṭo 'asmi varaṃ vṛṇuta kāṅkṣitam|
dāsye 'ahaṃ tanmahāprajñā mā tūṣṇīṃ brūta sarvaśaḥ|| 122.58||
devā ūcuḥ|
harireṣa mahādeva pāppaya hatamānasaḥ|
tām asya nirṇuda kṣipraṃ nīhāram iva bhāskaraḥ|| 122.59||
eṣa lokahitārthāya devānaṃ ca mahābalaḥ|
kurute karma deveśa pāpmānaṃ hyasya nāśaya|| 122.60||
vayaṃ ca samatāṃ tubhyaṃ gaṇatāṃ gaṇamadhyagāḥ|
labhema sarvadaiveśa yadi tvaṃ manyase vibho|| 122.61||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣām evaṃ tu vadatāṃ devānām ṛṣisattama|
uvāca bhagavāñcharvaḥ prahasan prītamānasaḥ|| 122.62||
viṣṇureṣa surāḥ sadyo mokṣyate pāpmayānayā|
pāpmā ceyaṃ mahābhāgā ūṣare saṃbhaviṣyati|| 122.63||
niryāsaścaiva vṛkṣāṇām apāṃ phenastathaiva ca|
mahoragāṇāṃ gandhaśca strīṇāṃ nindā tathaiva ca|| 122.64||
dikkṣitasya ca viprasya aśubhasyāvakīrtanam|
brāhmaṇānāṃ parīvādo gavām arikīrtanam|| 122.65||
agnerujvalanaṃ caiva nadīnāṃ bandha eva ca|
ya etāni naraḥ kuryādrāgamohasamanvitaḥ|
sa etāṃ prāpnuyālloke svayambhūrapi lokapaḥ|| 122.66||
yadā tu vasudevasya suto viṣṇurbhaviṣyati|
tadā sa rūpiṇīm enāṃ nara eṣopabhokṣyate|| 122.67||
tatropabhujya varado harerjātāṃ svasāṃ tadā|
vimuktaḥ pāpmayā bhūya imaṃ lokaṃ cariṣyati|| 122.68||
yathā tvasya svasāpīyaṃ naiva bādhāṃ kariṣyati|
tathā caratvayaṃ ghoraṃ tapaḥ paramaduścaram|| 122.69||
yūyaṃ ca ṛṣibhiḥ sārdham ihaiva susamāhitāḥ|
puraścaraṇam avyagrāḥ kurudhvaṃ madanujñayā|| 122.70||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā devena devāḥ sarve tadā harim|
ūcuḥ kuru tapo ghoraṃ tataḥ śreyo hyavāpsyasi|| 122.71||
tataḥ sa candraṃ śailendram āruhya susamāhitaḥ|
tapaścacāra sumahadindriyagrāmatāpanam|| 122.72||
devā api mahātmāna ṛṣibhiḥ saha suvrataiḥ|
hiraṇyavarṇe śailendre tapastepuḥ samāhitāḥ|| 122.73||
atha teṣāṃ samāpte tu vrate tasmin pinākadhṛk|
ādideśa vrataṃ dīptaṃ yat tat pāśupataṃ mahat|| 122.74||
uvāca sa tu tuṣṭātmā ābhāṣya murapuṃgavān|
meghadundubhinirghosaṃ dhīrambhīraśabdavat|| 122.75||
devadeva uvāca|
puraścaraṇam etaddhi sucīrṇaṃ lokapāḥ svayam|
idaṃ pāśupataṃ cīrtvā nirvṛtā yātanirbhayāḥ|| 122.76||
etat paraṃ pavitraṃ ca sāṃkhyayogādhikaṃ vratam|
nāsmāt parataraṃ kiṃcit sūkṣmaṃ vā vidyate kvacit|| 122.77||
bhasmanā digdhasarvāṅgo digvāsāḥ śucireva ca|
śarīrasthairyajan rudraṃ sarvam upāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 122.78||
ārdrasnānāt paraṃ bhasma ārdre jantuvadho dhruvam|
ārdraṃ tu prakṛtiṃ vidyāt prakṛtiṃ cāpi bandhanam|| 122.79||
prakṛtestu prahāṇārthaṃ bhasmanā snānam iṣyate|
digvāsastvaṃ ca śaucaṃ ca yena jāyenna karhicit|| 122.80||
yantrāṇāṃ paramaṃ yantram anyadyasmānna vidyate|
ṣaḍaṅgaṃ sarvakāmīyaṃ sarvalokanamaskṛtam|| 122.81||
śuci sarvapavitraṃ ca sarvapāpāpahaṃ śubham|
tapaso vardhanaṃ caiva te carantu samāhitāḥ|
yantraṃ tvapāpaṃ vijñeyaṃ prakṛtiḥ sā ca saṃsmṛtā|| 122.82||
bandhaśca trividhaḥ proktaḥ sanyāsaphalam eva ca|
tasmāt sarvaprahāṇārthaṃ yantram etat samācaret|| 122.83||
asaṃmataḥ sadā loke yena jīryenna karhicit|
yogaṃ ca paramaṃ prāpya yogānāṃ yat paraṃ mahat|| 122.84||
yasmāt parataraṃ nāsti ṣaḍaṅgaṃ sarvakāmikam|
yena muktaḥ patedbhūyo na yogī maraṇādiṣu|| 122.85||
taṃ yogaṃ samanuprāpya siddho divyena karmaṇā|
na lipyate mahāyogī karmabhistu kṛtākṛtaiḥ|| 122.86||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ te devadevena samājñaptā divaukasaḥ|
samāpya tadvrataṃ ghoraṃ śaṃkarasya gaṇā babhuḥ|| 122.87||
te gaṇatvam anuprāpya tasya devasya śūlinaḥ|
anvagṛhaṇanta taṃ deśaṃ tapasā bhāvitā bhṛśam|| 122.88||
devā ūcuḥ|
yasmādiha sucīrṇaṃ naḥ puraścaraṇam antaśaḥ|
tasmādidaṃ maheśasya guhyam āyatanaṃ smṛtam|| 122.89||
puriścandram iti khyātaṃ triṣu lokeṣu dīptimat|
pañcayojanavistīrṇaṃ tāvadevāyataṃ śubham|| 122.90||
siddhacāraṇasaṃkīrṇam apsarogaṇanāditam|
bahupakṣininādanṃ ca nadīprasravaṇākulam|
bhaviṣyati mahāpuṇyaṃ tapodhanatapovanam|| 122.91||
yo 'atrāgatya caruṃ kṛtvā bhojayitvā ca brāhmaṇam|
arcayeddevadeveśaṃ rudraloke sa modate|| 122.92||
yaścātra niyamaṃ kṛtvā bhasmasnāyī yatavrataḥ|
muhūrtam api tiṣṭheta sa gacchedgaṇamadhyatām|| 122.93||
akṣayaścāmaraścaiva jarārogavivarjitaḥ|
rudrasya gaṇapo bhūtvā yogaiśvaryam avāpsyati|| 122.94||
kāmacārī supāpātmā yo 'apyatra divasaṃ vaset|
so 'aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|| 122.95||
sakāmo 'api durācāro yo 'atra praṇān parityajet|
so 'api devasadaḥ prāpya devaiḥ saha cariṣyati|| 122.96||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste daivatāḥ sarve prāpya tat paramaṃ tapaḥ|
ijyāsnānaṃ tadā cakrurīśasya paramātmanaḥ|| 122.97||
atha te kṛtakṛtyāśca mahāyogabalānvitāḥ|
hariṃ prati manaścakrurgantuṃ sarve divaukasaḥ|| 122.98||
taṃ jvalantam ivādityam āgacchanto mahābalāḥ|
hariścandragirau vyāsa hariṃ dadṛśuravyayam|| 122.99||
so 'api kālena mahatā dhūtapāpmā mahātapāḥ|
tadaiva labdhvā devānāṃ samatāṃ muditātmavān|| 122.100||
-- -- prati tadā vegādutthāya ṛṣisattama|
śikharāt saṃnipatyāśu teṣāṃ madhye 'avatiṣṭhata|| 122.101||
tataste muditāḥ samyagghariṇā saha saṃgatāḥ|
śikharaṃ tadgirestasya phalena samayojayan|| 122.102||
yasmāddharirayaṃ hyatra candravannirmalo babhau|
tapasā mahatā caiva tasmādeṣo 'acaleśvaraḥ|| 122.103||
hariścandra iti khyāto bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|
yasmādaprakṛtenaiva prapāto 'atra kṛtaḥ punaḥ|
tasmādbhṛgurayaṃ loke puṇyo bhavatu sarvaśaḥ|| 122.104||
atra yo 'abhyetya deveśā bhṛguprapatanaṃ naraḥ|
sādhayeta sa gaccheta harerlokam atiprabham|| 122.105||
mahāpātakasaṃyukto vyādhinā samupadrutaḥ|
yo 'atra sādhayate prāṇān so 'api mucyenmahābhayāt|| 122.106||
yadvā prārthayate nityaṃ prapāte cātra kiṃcana|
tat prāpnuyānnaraḥ sarvam acirāt tacca vai smṛtam|| 122.107||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
hariścandram imaṃ yastu puriścandraṃ tu dharmavit|
paṭheta śṛṇuyādvāpi pāpmānaṃ viśasyati|| 122.108||
idaṃ tu yaḥ śuciranasūyavān sadā naraḥ paṭheddvijagaṇadevasaṃsadi|
sa nirmalo raviriva tejasā jvalaṃstriviṣṭape vasati yathāmaro varaḥ|| 122.109||
iti skandapurāṇe hariścandragirivarṇano nāma
dvāviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 122.122||

skandapurana123
sanatkumāra uvāca|
taṃ puriścandram āsādya sa rāmaḥ śaktinandana|
apaśyat parameśānam asuraiḥ kliṣṭamānasaḥ|| 123.1||
sa dṛṣṭvā tu mahādevaṃ sāmbaṃ sagaṇam avyayam|
praṇataḥ prāñjalirbhūtvā tasthau prahvastadāgrataḥ|| 123.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
so 'api devastadā prīto jāmadagnyaṃ mahāmanāḥ|
uvāca vacasāṃ yoniridaṃ gambhīraśabdavat|| 123.3||
kiṃśukairiva saṃchannaṃ candanenokṣitaṃ yathā|
tathā taṃ kṣatajenaiva sarvataśca samukṣitam|
sravantaṃ gairikaṃ dhātum acalendram ivāparam|| 123.4||
devadeva uvāca|
jāmadagnya mahat karma kṛtaṃ surahitepsayā|
tvayā putrādya saṃgrāme saiṃhikeyān vinighnatā|| 123.5||
tavānena mahābāho karmaṇā paritoṣitaḥ|
prayacchāmi varān sapta tān vadasva yathecchasi|| 123.6||
rāma uvāca|
bhagavan yadi tuṣṭo 'asi mama dehi svayaṃ prabho|
sarvajñānasamutpattiṃ sarvavedapravarttitām|| 123.7||
avadhyaḥ syām ahaṃ yuddhe dhanurvedaṃ ca yaccha me|
paraśuṃ sarvahantāram asaṅgaṃ ratham eva ca|| 123.8||
astragrāmaṃ ca vipulam amaratvaṃ tathākṣayam|
varān mahyam imān deva prayacchasva namastava|| 123.9||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyaivaṃ vadato vyāsa prahasya bhagavān haraḥ|
uvāca sarvam etat te bhaviṣyati mamājñayā|| 123.10||
dhanurvedavrataṃ caiva varṣam ekaṃ cariṣyasi|
tasmādihaiva vastavyaṃ tvayā bhṛgukulodvaha|| 123.11||
tatastasmai sa bhagavān svayam eva trilocanaḥ|
ādideśa vrataṃ ghoraṃ cacāra sa ca saṃyataḥ|| 123.12||
samāpte tu vrate devaḥ svayam āgamya yajñahā|
dhanurvedaṃ dadau tasmai samantraṃ sahasaṃgraham|| 123.13||
saśulvaṃ saparistomaṃ sodyamaṃ sānukarṣaṇam|
astragrāmaṃ ca vipulaṃ pratyastrasahitaṃ tathā|| 123.14||
prādāt tasmai tadeśāna idam covāca susvaram|
ayaṃ tvayā dhanurvedaḥ sahāstraiḥ sumahābala|| 123.15||
kṣatriyebhyo na dātavya iti macchāsanaṃ smara|
yadi ceddāsyase mohāt kṣatriyebhyaḥ kadācana|
laghutvaṃ yāsyase teṣāṃ yuddhe cāpi jayo na te|| 123.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa paraśuṃ datvā rathaṃ kāmagam eva ca|
manasā cintite yuktam upatiṣṭhantam akṣayam|| 123.17||
yantṛṇā yakṣarājena amareṇābhisambhṛtam|
jagāmādarśanaṃ tasya sahasaiva pinākadhṛk|| 123.18||
so 'api labdhvā varān vyāsa jagāma piturantikam|
na cāpaśyata taṃ tatra kārtavīryasutairhatam|| 123.19||
akṛtvā tasya kartavyaṃ so 'api rāmaḥ pratāpavān|
niḥkṣatrāṃ pṛthivīṃ cakre saptakṛtvaṃ ca satrikam|| 123.20||
rudhireṇa sa toṣāṃ ca hradān sapta cakāra ha|
samantapañcake vyāsa pitR̥ṃstenābhyatarpayat|| 123.21||
tataśca kṛtvā niḥkṣatrāṃ pṛthivīṃ bhṛgusattamaḥ|
mahādevaprasādāt tu trailokyasyeśvaro babhau|| 123.22||
taṃ śrīstuṣṭirdhṛtiścaiva siddhiḥ kīrtiryaśastathā|
śraddhā medhā tathā kṣāntiranasūyā prasaṃyamaḥ|| 123.23||
ūhā hyapohā tarkaśca damaśca śama eva ca|
rūpiṇyo bhārgavaṃ sarvā mātaraḥ samupasthitāḥ|| 123.24||
tān sarvān sa tadā prāha viśadhvaṃ mām aśaṅkitāḥ|
śrīriyaṃ tu durācārā dūra evāvatiṣṭhatām|| 123.25||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
taṃ tathāvādinaṃ sādhvī uvāca śrīrmahābalam|
kimarthaṃ māṃ mahābāho nābhinandasi durlabhām|| 123.26||
rāma uvāca|
capalā madanīyā ca adhruvā cāsi śobhane|
atastvāṃ nābhinandāmi mama tvaṃ dūrato bhava|| 123.27||
tvayāviṣṭo naraḥ sarvo yadi syāt svayam īśvaraḥ|
aiśvaryamadasammūḍha akāryeṣveva vartate|| 123.28||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa rājā bhārgavaḥ śrīmān yajñairīje mahāmanāḥ|
adho 'agamacca pṛthivī tasya yajñe purā dvija|| 123.29||
vyāsa uvāca|
kimarthaṃ pṛthivī tasya yajñe pātālam āviśat|
kāraṇaṃ tatra kiṃ manye etadicchāmi veditum|| 123.30||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa gatvā pṛthivīpālaḥ kaśyapaṃ munisattamam|
uvāca mama hotā tvaṃ bhava sattvavatāṃ vara|| 123.31||
taṃ tathāvādinaṃ vyāsa tadovāca narādhipam|
kaśyapaḥ kupitastatra nindamāno bhṛgūttamam|| 123.32||
patitastvaṃ durācāro bhinnaśīlaḥ supāpakṛt|
kathaṃ vā yājayiṣyāmi bhrūṇavadhyābhikāriṇam|| 123.33||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa tena vākyena uvāca ṛṣisattamam|
viṣaye mama mā tiṣṭha tvam adya munisattama|| 123.34||
svāmyahaṃ jagato vipra nāhaṃ yatra tato vraja|
tataḥ sa tasya taṃ deśaṃ parityajyāvrajat tadā|| 123.35||
nāsasāda ca taṃ deśaṃ yatrāsau na bhavet prabhuḥ|
anāsādayamānaśca aṭavīm āśritastadā|
antardhānagato bhūtvā cacāra bahulāḥ samāḥ|| 123.36||
athāpaśyat samāsīnaṃ kapotaṃ vṛkṣasaṃsthitam|
anaṅgenābhisambaddhaṃ kapotyā hāryatāṃ gatam|| 123.37||
kapota uvāca|
yadāprabhṛti suśroṇi mayā dṛṣṭāsi śobhane|
tadāprabhṛti śuṣyāmi ratiṃ nāpnomi śobhane|| 123.38||
kapotyuvāca|
maivaṃ brūyā durācāra adharmyaṃ hi kadācana|
kapota uvāca|
na ceddāsyasi me 'atra tvaṃ balāt tvāhaṃ sumadhyame|
svīkariṣyāmi yacchasva nato 'asmi tava pādayoḥ|| 123.39||
kapotyuvāca|
kiṃ na te 'asti bhayaṃ krūra jāmadagnyānmahābalāt|
yena tvaṃ vardhase 'adyeha patihīnāṃ pativratām|| 123.40||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evamuktaḥ sa tu tayā kapotaḥ śaktinandana|
uvāca rāmaḥ ko 'ayaṃ vai mama tulyo na kenacit|| 123.41||
tasyaivaṃ vadatastatra rāmanāmāṅkitastadā|
bāṇaḥ śiro jahārāśu kaśyapastadapaśyata|| 123.42||
sa taṃ dṛṣṭvā tathāvṛttaṃ bhītastasmānmahābalāt|
yājayāmāsa rājānaṃ jāmadagnyaṃ mahāmanāḥ|| 123.43||
kaśyapa uvāca|
yājayāmyaham adyaiva rājan bhārgavasattama|
yadi cedīpsitāṃ me tvaṃ dadāsi śubhadakṣiṇām|| 123.44||
rāma uvāca|
yadbravīṣi na saṃdeho dātāhaṃ tanmahātapaḥ|
māṃ yājaya yathānyāyaṃ tavāsmyadya vaśe sthitaḥ|| 123.45||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastasyābhavadvyāsa sumahān bhūridakṣiṇaḥ|
yajño 'aśvamedho devānāṃ yatra tṛptirajāyata|| 123.46||
tasyātha dakṣiṇākāle jāmadagnyaḥ pratāpavān|
uvāca kaśyapaṃ brūhi dakṣiṇāṃ kāṃ dadāni te|| 123.47||
sa prāha pṛthivīṃ kṛtsnāṃ saśailavanakānanām|
dakṣiṇāṃ datsva mahyaṃ tvaṃ yacca te 'asti gṛhe vasu|| 123.48||
sa tasmai tat tathā kṛtvā viśuddhenāntarātmanā|
cīrāṇi ādāya taṃ prāha kaśyapaṃ kiṃ karomyaham|| 123.49||
kaśyapa uvāca|
imaṃ deśaṃ parityajya deśam anyaṃ prayāhi bho|
mama deśe na vastavyaṃ tvayādya bhṛgunandana|| 123.50||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam astviti procya kṛtvā cābhipradakṣiṇām|
jagāma saritāṃ yoniṃ samudraṃ varuṇālayam|| 123.51||
taṃ gatvā sāgaraṃ bhīmam uvāca bhṛgunandanaḥ|
mama deśaṃ prayacchasva nivāsāya mahodadhe|| 123.52||
samudra uvāca|
yojayasva yathānyāyaṃ bhavān mādya vaśe sthitaḥ|
velāsamīpe tvaṃ sthitvā vikṛṣya balavaddhanuḥ|
muñcasva sāyakaṃ rāma parīpsan deśam uttamam|| 123.53||
yāvat sa sāyakaḥ kṣiptastava prāṇasamīritaḥ|
yāsyate tāvadevāhaṃ pradāsyāmi tavālayam|| 123.54||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa bhṛguśārdūlaḥ kṛtvādaram atandritaḥ|
yuyoja sāyakaṃ vyāsa vikṛṣya balavaddhanuḥ|| 123.55||
kṛtvā manasi saṃkalpaṃ yojanānāṃ śataṃ tadā|
gamiṣyati mamāyaṃ vai athainam abhimantrayat|| 123.56||
sāgareṇa tadā śambhuḥ stutastadupaśāntaye|
surāṇāṃ hitakāmārthaṃ sāgarāśoṣaṇāya ca|| 123.57||
taṃ kṣiptaṃ jāmadagnyena rurodhāpratimaṃ śaram|
sa rudro yojanānyetya nyapataddvādaśaiva tu|| 123.58||
tāvacca deśam udadhirvisasarja hasanniva|
āvasacca mahātejā jāmadagnyo 'api taṃ tathā|| 123.59||
taṃ deśaṃ bhṛgutanayaḥ surendrakalpo hṛṣṭātmā mṛgagaṇapakṣisaṃghajuṣṭam|
siṃhendradvipaśarabharkṣaghoranādaṃ śrīmantaṃ puram iva devatā cakāra|| 123.60||
iti skandapurāṇe rāmamāhātmye trayoviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 123.123||

skandapurana124
sanatkumāra uvāca|
jāmadagnyena sā dattā tathā pṛthvī mahātmane|
giriśṛṅga ivāpātādadhastāt sā tadāvrajat|| 124.1||
tām uvāca muniḥ kruddhastiṣṭha tiṣṭha vasuṃdhare|
kimarthaṃ māṃ parityajya adhastādvrajase śubhe|| 124.2||
pṛthivyuvāca|
jāmadagnyaṃ vinā rāmaṃ priyaṃ patim atidyutim|
na śaknomi mune sthātuṃ tadguṇāhṛtacetanā|| 124.3||
yadi mā yacchase 'adya tvaṃ rāmāya munipuṃgava|
yāsyāmyaham adho nātha na tiṣṭheyam ato 'anyathā|| 124.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyāstadvacanaṃ śrutvā kaśyapastapyatāṃ varaḥ|
uvāca vasudhāṃ kruddho dahanniva tadaujasā|| 124.5||
kaśyapa uvāca|
gaccha tvaṃ sudurācāre adhaḥ punaravāggatim|
vasudhāhaṃ bhaviṣyāmi paśya me tapaso balam|| 124.6||
tataḥ sa bhagavān vyāsa yogaṃ paramam āsthitaḥ|
pṛthivītvam anuprāpto dhārayāmāsa mānuṣān|| 124.7||
bahūnyabdasahasrāṇi yadasau pṛthivī babhau|
tadā pṛthvī viṣaṇṇā taṃ prasādayata kaśyapam|| 124.8||
pṛthivyuvāca|
bhagavaṃstapasā tubhyaṃ yogena ca balena ca|
na kaścidapi tulyo 'asti divi vā bhuvi vā vibho|| 124.9||
prasādaye tvāṃ śirasā dṛṣṭaṃ te balam uttamam|
yanmayāpakṛtaṃ kiṃcit tat kṣamasva mahāmune|| 124.10||
aham eva hi lokeṣu pṛthivī syāṃ tavājñayā|
dīnāyā mama viprendra prasādaṃ kartum arhasi|| 124.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tāṃ tathopasthitāṃ dṛṣṭvā bhagavānṛṣisattamaḥ|
uvāca prahasan devīṃ pṛthivīṃ praṇatāṃ tadā|| 124.12||
tavaiva hyapacāreṇa mayedaṃ kṛtam īdṛśam|
tvam idānīṃ mayā dattaṃ pṛthivītvaṃ samācara|| 124.13||
mama tvaṃ duhitṛtvaṃ ca gatvā kaśyapavaṃśajā|
kāśyapī viditā loke bhaviṣyasi vasuṃdhare|| 124.14||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sā pṛthivī vyāsa adho gatvā punaḥ sthitaḥ|
pṛthivītvaṃ samāsādya babhūva vigatajvarā|| 124.15||
ya imaṃ pṛthivībhāvaṃ kaśyapasya mahāmuneḥ|
pṛthivyāgamanaṃ caiva punarbhāvaṃ tathaiva ca|| 124.16||
śṛṇuyāt paṭhate vāpi śucirbhūtvā sadaiva hi|
sa labhetākṣayā/llokān pṛthivīphalam eva ca|| 124.17||
tāṃ sarvalokaprabhavām anekaśo mune praṇamyeha sadā narottamaḥ|
prakīrtayedyo vasudhāṃ vasupradāṃ sa lokam āpnoti ṛṣerathākṣayam|| 124.18||
iti skandapurāṇe kaśyapasya pṛthivībhāvo nāma
caturviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 124.124||

skandapurana125
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi dhvajasaṃgrāmam ūrjitam|
devānām asurāṇāṃ ca porāṇayogavināśanam|| 125.1||
āsīddanusutaḥ śrīmān vipracittirmahābalaḥ|
tapastepe sa yuktātmā bhastrāpada iti śrutiḥ|| 125.2||
sa rādhya tatra deveśaṃ bhagavantaṃ trilocanam|
varaṃ vavre 'amaratvaṃ ca tasmai prādāt sa devapaḥ|| 125.3||
dhvajaṃ māyāmayaṃ divyaṃ sarvagaṃ kāñcanaṃ śubham|
uvāca cainaṃ tuṣṭātmā bhagavān dānaveśvaram|| 125.4||
ayaṃ tava danoḥ putra viśvarūpo dhvajottamaḥ|
enam āśritya yuddheṣu tvam ajayyo bhaviṣyasi|| 125.5||
amaraśca mahābāh0 śabdaṃ cenna kariṣyasi|
ato 'anyathā tu te bhāgyairbhavitā vijayo raṇe|| 125.6||
sa evam ukto devena dhvajena mahatā yudhi|
danujaiḥ saha viprendra devān sarvān samāhvayat|| 125.7||
tadyuddham abhavadghoraṃ tumulaṃ lomaharṣaṇam|
varṣāṇāṃ tu śatānyaṣṭau daśa caiva sudāruṇam|| 125.8||
tatrādbhutam apaśyante danuputrasya dhīmataḥ|
dhvajena viśvarūpeṇa yadeko nyavadhīdbahūn|| 125.9||
yudhyataścāsya saṃgrāme dhvajam āśritya māyayā|
na devāḥ praharantyasya paśyamānāstu mohitāḥ|| 125.10||
nāpaśyante danusutān nāpi daityāṃstathā raṇe|
dhvajam evābhipaśyanti sarve mūḍhā divaukasaḥ|| 125.11||
mumucuryānyamoghāni āyudhāni divaukasaḥ|
tāni channānyabhūvan hi dhvajachāyāmilena vai|| 125.12||
agrataḥ pṛṣṭhataścaiva pārśvayorūrdhvam eva ca|
dhvajam evābhipaśyanti na daityān nāpi dānavān|| 125.13||
tatra te sāyakāstīkṣṇā jvalantaḥ pāvakārciṣaḥ|
niḥsṛtya tu dhvajādvyāsa dārayanti surottamān|| 125.14||
gadāśca parighāścaiva bhindipālāḥ satomarāḥ|
niḥsṛtāni tathānyāni dṛśyante 'astrāṇi vai dhvajāt|| 125.15||
te devāstena daityena dhvajam āśritya sarvaśaḥ|
bhagnā vicetasaḥ saṃkhye kṛtā naṣṭaparākramāḥ|| 125.16||
tān bhagnān bhajyamānāṃśca sarvān dṛṣṭvā surottamām|
jagarja jalado yadvaddhvajam āśritya dānavaḥ|| 125.17||
tasya tacchidram ālakṣya bhagavān pākaśāsanaḥ|
dhvajam ālakṣya cikṣepa vajraṃ paramamanyumān|| 125.18||
jvaladādityasaṃkāśaṃ tadvajraṃ bhīmaśabdavat|
sadhvajaṃ dānaveśānam akarodyamagocaram|| 125.19||
dhvaje lakṣyaṃ samāviśya devendreṇa mahātmanā|
hatāste dānavāḥ sarve sahasrāṇi caturdaśa|| 125.20||
te tena śabdena mahānubhāvā hatāḥ samālakṣya surendrakalpāḥ|
dhvaje niveśyaindrasamānacihnā vajreṇa devendrabalena sarve|| 125.20||
iti skandapurāṇe dhvajayuddhe pañcaviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 125.125||

skandapurana126
vyāsa uvāca|
bhastrāpadam iti proktaṃ tvayā brahmasutāvyaya|
kathaṃ tadabhavat sthānam etadicchāmi veditum|| 126.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ikṣvākukulasambhūto bāhurnāma prajeśvaraḥ|
haihayaistālajaṅghaiśca tasya rājyam aśeṣataḥ|
hṛtaṃ viprendra vikramya sabhāryaḥ sa vanaṃ yayau|| 126.2||
sa ṛcīkāśramaṃ gatvā ṛcīkenānupālitaḥ|
uvāsa vanamadhye tu garbhiṇyā bhāryayā saha|| 126.3||
tasyāḥ prasavakāle tu bhāryāyāḥ śaktinandana|
sapatnyā rāgamohena garo 'asyai sampradāpitaḥ|| 126.4||
sā tena vedanāṃ prāpya tapyamānā rujānvitā|
śītaṃ toyam iti procya mūrchitā nyapatadbhuvi|| 126.5||
tāṃ tathā patitāṃ dṛṣṭvā sa rājā manyutāpitaḥ|
kumbham ādāya vṛddho 'api toyārthaṃ saritaṃ yayau|| 126.6||
sa pūrayitvā kumbhaṃ taṃ skandhenādāya duḥkhitaḥ|
vṛddhabhāvācchramāccaiva papāta ca mamāra ca|| 126.7||
mṛto mṛta itītyevam ṛṣibhiḥ samudāhṛte|
sā devī mūrchitottasthau patiśokasamāhatā|| 126.8||
sā garasya ca tāpena patimṛtyukṛtena ca|
samāhatā tadā vyāsa kurarīva vyanādayat|| 126.9||
bāhostu ṛṣayaḥ sarve vasiṣṭhādyāḥ samāgatāḥ|
kṛtvā tu cayanaṃ samyak saṃskāram abhirocayan|| 126.10||
tam agniṃ praviśantī sā śaivyā garbheṇa dūṣitā|
vāritā ṛṣibhirvyāsa aurveṇa ca mahātmanā|| 126.11||
tasyāstatra dine vyāsa sāyāhne manyunāśanaḥ|
gareṇa saha garbho 'asau niḥsṛto 'analasaprabhaḥ|| 126.12||
tasmai sagara ityeva nāma cakre ṛṣistadā|
saṃskāraṃ cākarot tasya sarvam eva kṛpānvitaḥ|| 126.13||
dhanurvedaṃ dadau caiva vedān sāṅgāṃstathaiva ca|
astragrāmaṃ ca vipulaṃ rathaṃ cāsaṅgam avyayam|| 126.14||
sa tena rathamukhyena yudhi śatrūñjaghāna ha|
aurvāstraṃ caiva saṃdhāya teṣāṃ dharmam anāśayat|| 126.15||
sa hatvā tāṃstathā vyāsa prāpya rājyam athāpi ca|
vainateyasvasāṃ prāpya śaivyāṃ caiva sumadhyamām|| 126.16||
anapatyo mahābāhustryambakaṃ devasattamam|
ārādhayan mahātejāḥ putrahetornarādhipaḥ|| 126.17||
tasmai prādāt sa bhagavān putravaṃśakaraṃ prabhuḥ|
ṣaṣṭiṃ caiva sahasrāṇi sutānāṃ sumahātmanām|| 126.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
labhvā sa tu varaṃ rājā bhāryādvayam uvāca ha|
vainateyasvasāṃ caiva śaivyāṃ caiva mahāmanāḥ|| 126.19||
sagara uvāca|
mahyaṃ devena dattaśca putro vaṃśakaraḥ śubhaḥ|
ṣaṣṭiṃ caiva sahasrāṇi putrāṇāṃ sumahātmanām|| 126.20||
tatra kā vṛṇute devyau varaṃ devī śubhaṃ hitam|
brūta nāhaṃ vibhāgaṃ vaḥ karomi viditātmanām|| 126.21||
vainateyasvasovāca|
ṣaṣṭiḥ putrasahasrāṇi mama santu narādhipa|
śaivyābravīt suto mahyam eko vaṃśakaro 'astu vai|| 126.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
asamañjasutaṃ śaivyā tataḥ sā samprasūyata|
vainateyasvasāstumbaṃ mahāntaṃ samprasūyata|| 126.23||
tasmāt tumbāt tatastāni sahasrāṇi daśaiva tu|
guṇitāni vyāsa ṣaḍbhiḥ sambhavanta mahābalāḥ|| 126.24||
asamañjaḥ parityaktaḥ sagareṇa sutastataḥ|
adhārmika iti jñātvā anācāre vyavasthitaḥ|| 126.25||
aṃśumāṃstasya putrastu bāla evātidhārmikaḥ|
tasmin prītiṃ tadā cakre sagaro rājasattamaḥ|| 126.26||
asamañje parityakte hayamedhena dīkṣitaḥ|
ṣaṣṭiṃ tāni sahasrāṇi hayasyārakṣaṇe dadhau|| 126.27||
teṣāṃ hayaṃ cārayatām udyuktānāṃ mahātmanām|
antardhānagataḥ śakra ākṣipat taṃ hayottamam|| 126.28||
te lokān sarvaśo gatvā apaśyanto hayottamam|
pitaraṃ dīkṣitaṃ prāpya taṃ hayaṃ saṃnyavedayan|| 126.29||
sa saṃkruddhastadā rājā nirdahanniva tān sutān|
uvāca krodhatāmrākṣo naśyadhvaṃ kṣipram adya vai|| 126.30||
nāgantavyaṃ vinā vo 'adya hayaṃ krūrā vimārgata|
sutaiḥ kiṃ mama yuṣmābhiryāta sarve yamakṣayam|| 126.31||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā viprendra trailokyam akhilaṃ tadā|
vimṛgya khānayāmāsurimāṃ sarvāṃ vasuṃdharām|| 126.32||
diggajāṃste tato dṛṣṭvā ṛṣīṃśca niyatavratān|
dhārayanto 'avaniṃ sarvān dṛṣṭvā cābhipraṇamya ca|| 126.33||
kapilaṃ te muniṃ suptam avaikṣanta jalāśaye|
adūre 'asya hayaṃ caiva kruddhāste menire tadā|| 126.34||
preritā bhāvitārthena kāle pakvā mumūrṣavaḥ|
pitṛśāpādathocuste kapilaṃ munisattamam|| 126.35||
eṣa no hayamukhyasya hartā supto durātmavān|
enam adya vayaṃ sarve nayāma piturantikam|| 126.36||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste kālapāśena baddhāḥ sarve mahābalāḥ|
niyatervaśagāścaiva padbhistaṃ samatāḍayan|| 126.37||
sa tairabhyarditaḥ kruddhaḥ śaradām ayutaṃ tadā|
niruddhaṃ sahasā vāyum utsasarja yathāhirāṭ|| 126.38||
tasya vaktrādviniḥsṛtya sa vāyurjvalanātmakaḥ|
dadāha sāgarān sarvān nyāyadharmabahiṣkṛtān|| 126.39||
teṣu dagdheṣu sarveṣu ṛṣayo nāradādayaḥ|
sagarāya yathāvṛttam ācakhyuratiduṣkaram|| 126.40||
tataḥ sa rājā duḥkhārtaḥ saṃstabhyātmānam ātmanā|
aṃśumantaṃ priyaṃ pautram ādideśa mahāmanāḥ|| 126.41||
sagara uvāca|
imaṃ rathaṃ samāruhya gaccha taṃ hayam uttamam|
ihānaya mahābāho kālo no nātyagādyathā|| 126.42||
samācarethāstadvākyaṃ yathāsāvṛṣisattamaḥ|
krodhaṃ na kurute 'asmāsu tvayi naḥ saṃtatirdhruvā|| 126.43||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa evam ukto ratham āsthito nṛpo mahānubhāvaḥ surasiddhapūjitaḥ|
jagāma vegena surendravikramaḥ sa yatra yogī sagārantako babhau|| 126.44||
iti skandapurāṇe sagarotpātirnāma ṣaḍviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ||
126||

skandapurana127
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sa gatvā taṃ tadoddeśaṃ mahāgajaniṣevitam|
apaśyadbhasmabhūtāṃstān muniṃ ca jvalanaprabham|| 127.1||
tatastaṃ sa tadā vāgbhiḥ stavayuktābhirantike|
praṇamyākṣamāyat sarvaṃ pūrvairyadduṣkṛtaṃ kṛtam|| 127.2||
kapila uvāca|
rājannihāham ekānte yuktastiṣṭhāmi vijvaraḥ|
tairardito 'asmi sahasā vāyuṃ vaktrādavāsṛjam|| 127.3||
daśavarṣaśatāni sma saṃruddhaḥ so 'anilo mayā|
vimuktaḥ sahasā sarvāṃstān dadāha pitR̥ṃstava|| 127.4||
na buddhipūrvaṃ te dagdhā mayā rājan ruṣāpi vā|
hatāste kālapakvena phalenaiva yathā khagāḥ|| 127.5||
aśvo 'ayaṃ mama pārśvasthaḥ kenāpi viditātmanā|
hṛtasteṣāṃ vināśāya mā krudho nīyatāṃ hayaḥ|| 127.6||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tvanumate vyāsa aṃśumān sa narādhipaḥ|
pānīyam upacakrāma teṣāṃ dātuṃ mahāmanāḥ|| 127.7||
vainateyastam āhedaṃ svastrīyāṇāṃ mamodakam|
na dātavyaṃ mahābāho naitat teṣāṃ gamiṣyati|| 127.8||
aṃśumānuvāca|
kathaṃ me pitaraste vai lokān divyānavāpnuyuḥ|
etadicchāmi kathitaṃ tvayā kaśyapanandana|| 127.9||
vainateya uvāca|
devaloke sarit puṇyā gaṅgānāmāśubhāpahā|
tadambhobhistavāsthīni bandhūnām iha sarvaśaḥ|| 127.10||
saṃspṛṣṭāni yadā rājan tadaite mokṣam āpnuyuḥ|
aśubhādrājaśārdūla anyathā kiṃ jalena te|| 127.11||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ so 'aśvaṃ samādāya nivṛtto vyāsa bhūpatiḥ|
pitāmahāya pradadau tam aśvaṃ sukṛtātmavān|| 127.12||
so 'api rājā tadā prāpya hayamedhaṃ mahāmanāḥ|
samudranāśane buddhiṃ cakre sutavadhārditaḥ|| 127.13||
atha taṃ saritāṃ bhartā praṇamyābhiprasādya ca|
jagāma putratāṃ tasya idaṃ covāca taṃ tadā|| 127.14||
rājaṃstvadvaṃśajenāhaṃ kartavyaḥ kila suprabha|
yathāpūraṃ mahābāho pūrṇo gaṅgāmbhasā nṛpa|| 127.15||
mā krudhastava putro 'ahaṃ yaśaskṛd amitaprabha|
ratnāni ca pradāsyāmi śamam ehi mama prabho|| 127.16||
śāntaḥ krodhastatastasya samudraṃ prati bhūpateḥ|
viṣṇuścāsmai tadā tuṣṭaḥ pradadau īpsitān varān|| 127.17||
hayamedhaśataṃ sāgraṃ svarge vāsaṃ yathākṣayam|
vaṃśasya cākṣayaṃ nityaṃ yaśaścāgryaṃ tathākṣayam|| 127.18||
vayasyatvaṃ tathā caiva purāṃ dharme ca saṃsthitam|
etān varān sa labdhvā tu bhuktvā rājyam akaṇṭakam|| 127.19||
jagāma vanam evātha tapastaptvā tato divam|
tato 'aṃśumān babhau rājā dhārmikaḥ satyasaṃgaraḥ|| 127.20||
putraṃ rājye 'abhiṣicyaiva gaṅgāvataraṇāśayā|
tapastaptvā divaṃ yāto mahābalaparākramaḥ|| 127.21||
tato dilīpaḥ putro 'asya mahātmā devarāḍiva|
kṛtvā rājyaṃ yayau vyāsa vanam eva mahābalaḥ|| 127.22||
tatra gaṅgārtham udyuktastapastaptvā divaṃ gataḥ|
anavāpyaiva taṃ kāmam asya putro 'abhavat punaḥ|| 127.23||
rājā bhagīratho nāma jambūdvīpapatiḥ śubhaḥ|
dhārmikaḥ satyavāk śūro dharmo vigrahavāniva|| 127.24||
tasya janmaprabhṛtyeva hṛdaye munisattama|
sthitaṃ gaṅgāvataraṇaṃ kathaṃ kuryām iti prabho|| 127.25||
atha kālena mahatā kṛtvā sarvakriyāṃ nṛpaḥ|
tapastatāpa sumahadyenātuṣyajjagatprabhuḥ|| 127.26||
brahmā svayam athābhyetya tam uvāca yatavratam|
brūhi kiṃ te prayacchāni varān vṛṇu naradhipa|| 127.27||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa rājā taṃ dṛṣṭvā praṇamya hṛṣitānanaḥ|
uvāca dharmasyākṣayyaṃ svarge vāsaṃ tathākṣayam|| 127.28||
vaṃśaya cākṣayaṃ samyak putrāṇāṃ ca śataṃ varam|
śūrāṇāṃ dhārmikāṇāṃ ca samareṣvanivartitām|| 127.29||
jayaṃ ca yuddhe satataṃ loke kīrtiṃ tathākṣayām|
gaṅgāyāḥ saritaścāpi avatāram anuttamam|| 127.30||
bhāgīrathīti ca yathā loke khyātatamā bhavet|
etadicchāmi deveśa yadi tvaṃ manyase vibho|| 127.31||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktasya bhagavān sarvam etadaśeṣataḥ|
prādāt tasmai svayaṃ sraṣṭā idaṃ covāca taṃ nṛpam|| 127.32||
gaṅgāṃ tvaṃ rājaśārdūla svargānneṣyasi bhūtalam|
tāṃ patantīṃ divaḥ kaścicchakto dhāyituṃ na hi|
ṛte lokagurordevāt tryambakācchūlapāṇinaḥ|| 127.33||
tasmāt tvaṃ devadeveśam ārādhaya yatavrataḥ|
sa dhārayiṣyate vyaktaṃ varadānena te vibhuḥ|| 127.34||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktastu rājendro vāyubhakṣo 'animeṣaṇaḥ|
nirūcchvāso 'abhavat tatra himavacchikhare śubhe|| 127.35||
tasya varṣasahasreṇa tatparasya tadāśiṣaḥ|
tutoṣa bhagavān devaḥ kapardī nīlalohitaḥ|| 127.36||
varado 'asmīti cāpyuktvā ityuvāca punaḥ prabhuḥ|
divyaṃ cakṣuḥ prayacchāmi paśya māṃ rājasattama|| 127.37||
sa taṃ dṛṣṭvā maheṣvāsaṃ tridṛṣṭiṃ devam īśvaram|
uvāca saritaṃ deva dhārayasva varaṃ vṛṇe|| 127.38||
gaṅgāṃ tripathagāṃ divyāṃ yadi me tuṣyase 'avyaya|
mama kāmo mahādeva mṛtān pūrvapitāmahān|| 127.39||
svargaṃ nayeyaṃ nirayāt tārayitvātha tān śubhān|
teṣām arthe mahādeva prayāso 'ayaṃ mayā kṛtaḥ|
prasādāt tava te svargaṃ gaccheyurgaṅgayāplutāḥ|| 127.40||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bhagavān govṛṣadhvajaḥ|
uvāca rājaśārdūlaṃ sutuṣṭenāntarātmanā|| 127.41||
devadeva uvāca|
bhagīratha tathā tat te bhaviṣyati na saṃśayaḥ|
matprasādācca gaṅgā te duhitā sā bhaviṣyati|| 127.42||
dhārayiṣye tvadarthe ca tāṃ patantīṃ triviṣṭapāt|
vismāpanāya lokānāṃ hitārthaṃ ca nṛpottama|| 127.43||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā gaṅgā sā saritāṃ varā|
uvāca ko dhārayitvā mama vegaṃ surottamaḥ|| 127.44||
ahaṃ taṃ sahasaivādya gṛhītvāśu suduḥsahā|
gamiṣyāmi na saṃdehaḥ pātālaṃ sudurāsadam|| 127.45||
svayambhūryadyasau brahmā śakro vāpi sureśvaraḥ|
viṣṇurvāpyaditeḥ putro nayāmyeva na śaṃśayaḥ|| 127.46||
adya paśyantu me lokā mahadvegaṃ durāsadam|
patantyā bhuvi durdharṣam evaṃ sā saridabravīt|| 127.47||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyāstadvacanaṃ śrutvā sāvalepaṃ ca śaṃkaraḥ|
cakāra nigrahītuṃ tāṃ saṃkalpaṃ saritāṃ varām|| 127.48||
tasya saṃkalpamātreṇa devān vai jvara āviśat|
mamlurmālyāni sarveṣām utpātāścaiva jajñire|| 127.49||
viparyayo 'abhūllokānāṃ vimānāni ca petire|
asurāśca balonmattā dṛśyante 'atimahābalāḥ|
āhvayanto diteḥ putrān jvalanādityavarcasaḥ|| 127.50||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vaikṛtaṃ tadathālakṣya devā ūcuḥ śatakratum|
viparyayo 'ayaṃ nākasmācchīghraṃ vijñāyatāṃ prabho|| 127.51||
sammohaścābhavat tasya devasya ṛṣibhiḥ saha|
tasmin kāle samāgamya brahmā tānavabodhayat|| 127.52||
brahmovāca|
mā viṣaṇṇāvatiṣṭhadhvaṃ yūyaṃ sarve divaukasaḥ|
yadbravīmi nibodhadhvaṃ kālo mā vo 'atigādayam|| 127.53||
eṣa devo maheṣvāsaḥ kapardī meghavāhanaḥ|
gaṅgāṃ nāśayituṃ buddhim akarodbhīmavikramaḥ|| 127.54||
tenaivaṃ manasā devāścintite lokanāśane|
viparyayo yathā na syāt tathā kuruta mā ciram|| 127.55||
mayā saha ito gatvā ṛṣibhiḥ saha saṃgatāḥ|
āpadbhāvena deveśaṃ śaraṇaṃ yāta śaṃkaram|| 127.56||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te sahaiva tadā devā brahmaṇā padmayoninā|
jagmurhimavataḥ kūṭaṃ sarvaratnavibhūṣitam|| 127.57||
nāmnā hiraṇmayaṃ nāma yatra hairaṇvatī nadī|
apaśyanta ca taṃ devāstapobhaktyā sureśvaram|| 127.58||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te taṃ kruddham ivālakṣya yugāntānalasaprabham|
durnirīkṣyaṃ tadā vyāsa devīṃ śaraṇam āgatāḥ|| 127.59||
devā ūcuḥ|
sadevatānāṃ lokānāṃ jananyasi vibhāvari|
ato 'asi bhastrā rudrāṇi yaccha no 'abhayadaṃ padam|| 127.60||
śaraṇāgatā vayaṃ mātaḥ putrāstava vayaṃ śubhe|
rakṣa no devadeveśe etadicchāmahe vayam|| 127.61||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣāṃ tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bhītānāṃ śaraṇaiṣiṇām|
devānām abhayadaṃ devī dadau varam anuttamam|| 127.62||
tatastvaṃ devadeveśaṃ bhagavantaṃ pinākinam|
praṇamya śirasovāca bhītavat sācalātmajā|| 127.63||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tāṃ bhītāṃ praṇatāṃ devaḥ pādayorgatamūrdhajām|
utthāpayāmāsa tadā pāṇinābjadalatviṣā|| 127.64||
uvāca ca tadā sādhvīṃ bhītāsi himavatsute|
kimarthaṃ kiṃ ca te subhru bhayaṃ brūhi śubhānane|| 127.65||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
uvāca taṃ tadā vyāsa bhītavat himavatsutā|
dṛḍhaṃ bhītāsmi te deva rūpaṃ dṛṣṭvātibhāsvaram|| 127.66||
saṃvartakānalaprakhyaṃ durnirīkṣyaṃ surairapi|
lokā viṣaṇṇā deveśa devāśca ṛṣibhiḥ saha|| 127.67||
upāsate bhītabhītāḥ sarva ete sureśvarāḥ|
bhītāhaṃ te mahādeva matto 'adhikam ime surāḥ|| 127.68||
māṃ caiva śaraṇaṃ prāptāsteṣāṃ tvam abhayaṃ diśa|
tvaṃ kartā sarvalokānāṃ devānām ṛṣibhiḥ saha|
mā vināśaya tān kṛtvā yāce tvāṃ śirasā natā|| 127.69||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasyāstadvacanaṃ śrutvā devān dṛṣṭvā ca yajñahā|
uvāca na bhayaṃ vo 'asti mattastridaśasattamāḥ|| 127.70||
iyaṃ tu strīsvabhāvena himavattanaye sarit|
mayi duṣṭaṃ manaḥ kṛtvā patiṣyati mamopari|| 127.71||
tām ahaṃ saṃnirotsyāmi patantīṃ saritaṃ divaḥ|
yūyam api ālayān svān svānviśrabdhā vrajatānaghāḥ|| 127.72||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tatastadvacaḥ śrutvā praṇatā vibudhottamāḥ|
ūcuḥ prāñjalayo bhūtvā vācā te lajjamānayā|| 127.73||
devā ūcuḥ|
eṣā lokahitārthāya tvayā sṛṣṭā saridvarā|
capalāḥ saritaścaiva strīsvabhāvaśca tādṛśaḥ|| 127.74||
saiṣā tena svabhāvena asmākaṃ cābhisaṃśrayāt|
garvaṃ mahāntam āsthāya katthate hyakutobhayā|| 127.75||
garvo 'ayaṃ ca yatastasyā yena sā katthate nadī|
tannaḥ śṛṇuṣva deveśa mā krudho bhīmavikrama|| 127.76||
kāryārthaṃ prārthyamāno hi sarvo bhavati garvitaḥ|
loke tanurapi svāmin kim uteyaṃ saridvarā|| 127.77||
saiṣā sarinmahādeva dhāraṇāyepsitā tvayā|
sarvaśreṣṭhena devena garvitā katthate tataḥ|| 127.78||
tvayā daivatanāthena dhāriteyaṃ saridvarā|
puṇyā bhavitrī loke 'asmin sarvakilbiṣanāśanī|| 127.79||
yaḥ kaścit pātinīm enāṃ saritaṃ devatādhipa|
śakto dhārayituṃ devo na tu śreyo bhavet tataḥ|| 127.80||
tasmāt tvaṃ yācito devai rājñā cānena kālahan|
dhārayasva nadīm enāṃ śivo bhūtvā surottama|| 127.81||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ sa bhagavān devaistathyaṃ bahvavirodhi ca|
uktaḥ sabrahmakairdevaḥ sanārāyaṇalokapaiḥ|| 127.82||
rājño varapradānaṃ ca tadavekṣya punaḥ punaḥ|
uvāca devān deveśa idaṃ gambhīraśabdavat|| 127.83||
etaṃ rājānam uddiśya kṣudhāparyākulendriyam|
bhavatāṃ caiva mānyānāṃ vacanāddevasattamāḥ|| 127.84||
na nāśayiṣye saritam idaṃ tu śṛṇutānaghāḥ|
yadbravīmi mahāsattvā garvasyāsya vināśanam|| 127.85||
parvatendro 'asya garvasya vighāto bhavitā mahān|
anujahnuśca dharmātmā garvaṃ nāśayitā punaḥ|| 127.86||
macchāpopahatā ceyaṃ durācārā mahānadī|
patiṃ mānuṣam āsādya putrān sapta nihaṃsyati|| 127.87||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evam uktvā tataḥ śarvo devān daivatasattamaḥ|
uvāca brūta kiṃ vo 'anyaddadānyatha yathepsitam|| 127.88||
devā ūcuḥ|
bhagavan sthānam icchāmo devasya sumaharddhimat|
samantapañcakaṃ kṣetraṃ sadāvirahitaṃ tvayā|| 127.89||
bhastretyuktā yadasmābhirhimavattanayāvyayā|
padaṃ cābhayam icchanti tasmādbhastrāpadaṃ smṛtam|| 127.90||
yo 'atrāgacchenniyamavānarcayedvṛṣabhadhvajam|
so 'aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya rudralokam avāpnuyāt|| 127.91||
ahorātropavāsena caruṃ yaśca nivedayet|
sa nandīśvaratulyaste bhavitā devasattama|| 127.92||
prāṇān yaścātra deveśa tyajet saniyamo naraḥ|
athavāniyamāddeva yadṛcchāmaraṇena tu|| 127.93||
so 'api bhūtvā gaṇaistulyaḥ sthāsyati ābhūtasamplavam|
yukto divyena vapuṣā tavānucaratāṃ gataḥ|| 127.94||
namo bhastreśvarāyeti yaśca kṛtvā sadā śuciḥ|
uttiṣṭhedvā svapedvāpi śakraloke sa modate|| 127.95||
idaṃ mahaddivyam anantalābhaṃ paṭhet sadā yo dvijadevasaṃsadi|
mahānubhāvo gaṇapo mahājavo bhavet sa divyastava deva saṃśrayāt|| 127.96||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṅgāvatāre saptaviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 127.127||

skandapurana128
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasmin sabrahmakā devāḥ sthāṇoḥ sthāne manorame|
liṅgaṃ saṃsthāpya tīrthāni sarve cakruḥ pṛthak pṛthak|| 128.1||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- dityatīrthaṃ ca vikhyātaṃ cāśvamedhikam|| 128.2||
rudratīrthaṃ sthāṇutīrthaṃ brahmaṇastīrtham eva ca|
indratīrthaṃ vasūnāṃ ca aśvinoraparaṃ smṛtam|| 128.3||
yamasya cāparaṃ tīrthaṃ vāyostīrtham athāparam|
viṣṇoścāpyaparaṃ tīrthaṃ vikhyātaṃ surapūjitam|| 128.4||
snāta eteṣu viprarṣe caruṃ kṛtvā nivedya ca|
eṣu sthāneṣu divyeṣu carate hyakutobhayaḥ|| 128.5||
adyāpi tatra brahmarṣe śrūyate madhuraḥ svanaḥ|
mekhalāvalayonmiśro vaṃśavīṇāravotkaṭaḥ|| 128.6||
gāyantīnāṃ varāṅgīnāṃ nṛtyantīnāṃ tathaiva ca|
nityam apsarasāṃ vyāsa stuvantīnāṃ trilocanam|| 128.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste sahitā devā brahmaṇā devasattamam|
ūcuḥ paśyema bhagavannasyā dhāraṇam uttamam|| 128.8||
devadeva uvāca|
yatheṣṭaṃ śvaḥ prabhāte māṃ paśyadhvaṃ vibudheśvarāḥ|
dhārayantaṃ tripathagāṃ nadīṃ svaguṇagarvitām|| 128.9||
te tathoktāḥ praṇamyeśaṃ jagmurgaṅgāntikaṃ tadā|
uvāca tāṃ tato brahmā devīṃ lokasukhāvahām|| 128.10||
mā garvaṃ tvaṃ kṛthā gaṅge mā vināśam avāpnuhi|
ṛjubhāvaṃ samāsthāya patethāstvaṃ saridvare|| 128.11||
stuvatī tryambakaṃ somaṃ bhaktyā paramayā yutā|
tavākūtaṃ viditvāsau vināśāyodyataḥ prabhuḥ|| 128.12||
kṛcchreṇa toṣitaḥ śambhustavaiva hitakāmyayā|
māparādhaṃ kṛthā bhūyo lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā|| 128.13||
nāśāt tava saricchreṣṭhe dhruvaṃ lokakṣayo bhavet|
evaṃ te tāṃ samādhāya devāḥ sabrahmakāstadā|| 128.14||
dvitīye 'ahani lokeśāḥ smājagmurdidṛkṣavaḥ|
himavacchikharaṃ divyaṃ nāmnā vajropalaṃ mahat|| 128.15||
brahmā viṣṇurathānanto narā ṛṣaya eva ca|
ādityā vasavo rudrā aśvinau samarudgaṇāḥ|| 128.16||
sādhyā devāḥ sapitaro yakṣarākṣasapannagāḥ|
piśācāścāsurāścaiva śṛṅgiṇaḥ pṛśnayastathā|| 128.18||
ṛṣiratrirvasiṣṭhaśca marīciḥ pulahastathā|
pulastyaścāṅgirāścaiva bhṛguḥ kaśyapa eva ca|| 128.19||
auśijo vāmadevaśca gautamaśca mahatapāḥ|
cyavano 'atha bharadvāja indrapramatireva ca|| 128.20||
raibhyaśca jamadagniśca kuṇibāhuśca vīryavān|
atharvā śvetaketuśca dattātreyaśca viśrutaḥ|| 128.21||
rucirdharmaśca dakṣaśca sāvarṇī munayaśca ye|
agniśca vedabāhuśca śaṅkhapānnāmataśca yaḥ|| 128.22||
ambarīvāṃśca vikhyātaḥ ketumānapi cāparaḥ|
ete cānye ca bahava ṛṣayo devatāstathā|| 128.23||
vimānāni ca sarvāṇi gandharvāpsarasāṃ gaṇāḥ|
jambhakā ṛtavaścaiva nikāyāścaiva sarvaśaḥ|| 128.24||
tatrājagmurmudā yuktāḥ sarve paramavarcasaḥ|
teṣāṃ gaganasaṃsthānāṃ devānāṃ prekṣatāṃ tadā|| 128.25||
merumandarasaṃkāśa tasmiñchikharasattame|
umāsahāyo deveśaḥ sahasaivānvadṛśyata|| 128.26||
taḍijjvalanapiṅgena jaṭābhāreṇa rājatā|
ūrdhvasthitena mahatā bhagīratham uvāca saḥ|| 128.27||
devadeva uvāca|
bhagīratha kva sā gaṅgā pitR̥ṇāṃ tava tāraṇī|
samāhvaya mahābāho dhārayiṣye na saṃśayaḥ|| 128.28||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ sa rājaśārdūlaḥ smṛtvā tadbrahmaṇo vacaḥ|
sasmāra saritaṃ vyāsa śirasā prāñjalirnataḥ|| 128.29||
sā tena manasāhūtā svarlokanilayā nadī|
kṣaṇenābhyāyayau devī bhuvarlokaṃ śubhāvahā|| 128.30||
taṃ lokaṃ sā samāsādya manonilajavā nadī|
alaṃcakre mahāvegā sarvaṃ śubhaśatāraṇiḥ|| 128.31||
tataḥ sā tiryagāgamya ākāśasthā mahānadī|
ākāśagaṅgā saṃjajñe nāmnā oghavatīti vai|| 128.32||
ākāśagaṅgā sā bhūyo mahāvegā mahānadī|
śivam astu mametyevaṃ pāpātārdhapathāt tu sā|
śivagaṅgā tataḥ proktā nāmnā śivatarā hi sā|| 128.33||
kurvatī vipulaṃ śabdaṃ nadī vajrāśanisvanam|
yato devaiḥ samaṃ dṛṣṭā devagaṅgā tataḥ smṛtā|| 128.34||
tāṃ dṛṣṭvā munayaḥ sarve devalokāśca sarvaśaḥ|
jepuste sahasā śāntiṃ samprahṛṣṭatanūruhā|| 128.35||
teṣāṃ sā japatāṃ vyāsa nadī lokasukhāvahā|
stuvantī bhītabhīteva tridhā bhūtvāpatadbhuvi|| 128.36||
tāṃ patantīṃ mahādevastribhirvegairmahājavām|
jaṭābhāreṇa jagrāha devānām eva saṃnidhau|| 128.37||
taṃ jaṭābhāram āsādya sā trisrotā nirulbaṇā|
na tasyāntaṃ samāsede niruddhā yogamāyayā|| 128.38||
yasmāt sā bhītabhītā tu stuvantī patitā tadā|
tasmāt sā bhītagaṅgeti stotragaṅgeti cocyate|| 128.39||
tribhirvegaiśca patitā yasmāt sā sariduttamā|
trisroteti tataḥ sā vai procyate brahmavādibhiḥ|| 128.40||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sā tu tasmin nipatitā dhṛtā devena māyayā|
jaṭārandhraṃ vicinvānā uvāsa bahulāḥ samāḥ|| 128.41||
pūrṇaṃ sahasraṃ varṣāṇāṃ saṃsthitāṃ tāṃ jaṭāgṛhe|
devāstāṃ dadṛśuḥ sarve koṭarāntargām iva|| 128.42||
tataste sahasā devāḥ praṇipatya vṛṣadhvajam|
ūcurvimanaso vyāsa saritaṃ mā vināśaya|| 128.43||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
teṣām tadvacanaṃ śrutvā dṛṣṭvā rājānam eva ca|
vidudhāva jaṭābhāraṃ devadevo dayāmayaḥ|| 128.44||
vidhunvato jaṭābhāraṃ peturvai tatra bindavaḥ|
te muktāphalasaṃkāśāḥ pūrṇacandrāṃśunirmalāḥ|| 128.45||
cakrurbindusaro divyaṃ sāgarākāravarcasam|
tasmācchrotāṃsi saptaiva niḥsṛtāni mahānti ca|| 128.46||
nalinī hrādinī caiva plāvanī caiva pūrvagā|
sītā cakṣuśca sindhuśca tisrastā vai pratīcigāḥ|| 128.47||
madhyamaṃ tvanvagāt sroto rājā yena bhagīrathaḥ|
bhāgīrathīti sā gaṅgā procyate brahmavādibhiḥ|| 128.48||
dārayanto jagāmātha himavantaṃ saridvarā|
niruddhā himavatpāde ratnaśṛṅge śiloccaye|| 128.49||
tāṃ niruddhāṃ tato vīkṣya viṣaṇṇavadanastadā|
rājā bhagīratho vyāsa brahmāṇaṃ manasāsmarat|| 128.50||
tataḥ sa bhagavān brahmā supratīkaṃ mahāgajam|
uvāca dantavajrābhyāṃ dārayaināṃ śiloccayam|| 128.51||
sa yatra girirāḍbhinnaḥ supratīkena hastinā|
gaṅgādvāraṃ tu tat proktaṃ supuṇyaṃ caiva tat smṛtam|| 128.52||
gajaścābhimukho yāvannātiṣṭhata mahāyaśāḥ|
srotasā tāvadadhvānam ūḍho dvādaśayojanam|| 128.53||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
etat puṇyatamaṃ vyāsa gaṅgāvataraṇaṃ smṛtam|
sthānaṃ bhastrāpadaṃ nāma mayā yat parikīrtitam|| 128.54||
ya idaṃ śṛṇuyānmartyaḥ sadā parvasu parvasu|
sa devalokaṃ samprāpya devaiḥ saha cariṣyati|| 128.55||
idaṃ mahat pāpavimocanaṃ śubhaṃ vimānayānāpsarasāṃ vilambhanam|
śṛṇoti yo nityam adīnamānasaḥ sa yāti lokān viditān divaukasām|| 128.56||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṅgāvataraṇe aṣṭāviṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 128.128||

skandapurana129
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi hālāhalam aśeṣataḥ|
saṃgrāmaṃ ditiputrāṇāṃ devānāṃ ca bhayāvaham|| 129.1||
hālāhala iti khyāto gaṇo vikrāntapauruṣaḥ|
asurāṇāṃ babhau vyāsa dāruṇo brahmakaṇṭakaḥ|| 129.2||
gateṣu danuputreṣu sa gaṇaḥ krodhamūrchitaḥ|
balaṃ kṛtvā mukhaṃ sarvān devān yuddhe samāhvayat|| 129.3||
teṣāṃ teṣāṃ ca saṃgrāmaḥ sudhoraḥ samavartata|
asurāṇāṃ jayaścaiva sadaiva samapadyata|| 129.4||
tataste vibudhāḥ sarve vidarpā hatavikramāḥ|
hṛtarājyābhyagacchanta brahmāṇaṃ lokakāraṇam|| 129.5||
te tam ūcuśca saṃhatya hṛtarājyāḥ sma sāmpratam|
kathaṃ rājyaṃ punardeva labhema tava tejasā|| 129.6||
teṣāṃ śrutvā vacastadvai devaḥ salilasambhavaḥ|
uvāca devān deveśaṃ prasādayata mā ciram|| 129.7||
sa vo dātā mahāvīryo balaṃ devastrilocanaḥ|
yena tān samare sarvān vikrameṇa vijeṣyatha|| 129.8||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ta evam uktā deveśaṃ tapasārādhya śaṃkaram|
ūcuḥ prāñjalayo devā balaṃ no dehi yajñahan|| 129.9||
teṣāṃ tu japatām evaṃ tapasā toṣito haraḥ|
dadau mantram anādṛṣyaṃ sarvamantrottamaṃ haraḥ|| 129.10||
taṃ te samprāpya viprarṣe kṛtarakṣā divaukasaḥ|
amūḍhā mūḍhavat sarve asureṣvacaran tataḥ|| 129.11||
asurāstu tadā mūḍhān dṛṣṭvā sarvān divaukasaḥ|
amanyanta durācārā mūḍhā iti yathātatham|| 129.12||
hṛtarajyā ime devāḥ sarve mūḍhena cetasā|
unmattā vibhramantyevaṃ paśyataitān suretarāḥ|| 129.13||
ākrośanto 'apare tāṃstu abhijaghnuśca dāruṇam|
babandhuśca yathākāmaṃ mumucuśca tathāpare|| 129.14||
evaṃ teṣāṃ tadā vyāsa vartanāṃ śubhakarmaṇām|
sumahānabhavaddharmo 'asurāṇāṃ vyanīnaśat|| 129.15||
teṣāṃ tenāpacāreṇa asurāṇāṃ durātmanām|
dharmanāśādbalaṃ kṣīṇaṃ bubudhurdevatāgaṇāḥ|| 129.16||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste brahmaṇābhyuktāḥ sarve divyāstradhāriṇaḥ|
āhūyāsuraśārdūlān yuddhe sarvān nyasūdayan|| 129.17||
balo yatra hataḥ saṃkhye vajreṇa śataparvaṇā|
devendreṇābhivikramya balahā sa yataḥ smṛtaḥ|| 129.18||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
andhakārakam anyacca yuddham āsīt subhairavam|
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi śatāni ca punardaśa|| 129.19||
āsīddanusutaḥ śrīmān devatāntaka ityuta|
sa māyāṃ samparīpsan vai rudram ārādhayat purā|| 129.20||
tasmai varṣasahasreṇa varakāla upasthite|
brahmā dadau varaṃ vyāsa danoḥ putrāya dhīmate|| 129.21||
sa vavre tāmasīṃ māyāṃ sarvabhūtaprabādhanīm|
abhedyām anivāryāṃ ca yāṃ tu vetti na kaścana|| 129.22||
tasmai prādāt sa tāṃ māyām idaṃ covāca taṃ tadā|
bhaviṣyati hi māyeyaṃ yathoktā te mahābala|
kariṣyasi na cecchabdaṃ yathākāmaṃ danoḥ suta|| 129.23||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha labdhavaro vyāsa māyāchanno 'asurastataḥ|
bahubhirdānavaiḥ sārdhaṃ sarvā/llokānabādhata|| 129.24||
devā api bhayāt tasya nāvatiṣṭhan tadagrataḥ|
devāḥ sarve bhayodvignāstasthurnaiva tadagrataḥ|
sthānāni te parityajya yatra tatrāvatasthire|| 129.25||
āhūtāḥ krūraśabdena dānavairbaladarpitaiḥ|
tathāpi nāvatiṣṭhanta teṣām agre divaukasaḥ|| 129.26||
ṛṣayastānidaṃ prāpya ūcuḥ sarve pramanyavaḥ|
rakṣāṃ kuruta lokānāṃ māvalīnāvatiṣṭhata|| 129.27||
vayaṃ ca tapasā devā dhāryiṣyāma saṃyatāḥ|
mā bhayaṃ vo 'astu yudhyadhvaṃ kurudhvaṃ vijvaraṃ jagat|| 129.28||
ta evam uktāstairvyāsa ṛṣibhirlokakāraṇāt|
bhayānnaivāvatiṣṭhanta tasya dasyostadāgrataḥ|| 129.29||
yadā naivāvatiṣṭhante tathāpyuktā divaukasaḥ|
upāyam aparaṃ prāhustadā te munisattamāḥ|| 129.30||
āhūyāpsarasaḥ sarvā visṛjyantāṃ surottamāḥ|
kāmenāviṣṭamanasām asurāṇām upāntikam|| 129.31||
tāṃstāsu āsaktahṛdayān pītamaireyavihvalān|
vikramya haṃsyatha surā balādyuddhe balīyasaḥ|| 129.32||
tatastāḥ prahitā devairvañcanārthaṃ suradviṣām|
kvaṇannupūranirhrādakūjitotkarṇasārasāḥ|| 129.33||
pīnottuṅgastanābhogahāravikṣiptayaṣṭayaḥ|
vitrastabālahariṇīsadṛśāyatalocanāḥ|| 129.34||
calatkuṇḍalasaṃghṛṣṭapāṇḍarāgaṇḍamaṇḍalāḥ|
śikhikaṇṭacchaviharaślakṣṇavāsodharāḥ parāḥ|| 129.35||
pratyagravidrumacchedatāmroṣṭhādharapaṅktayaḥ|
vastrāntakusumāpīḍasaṃsaktakarapallavāḥ|| 129.36||
naikaratnaprabhākīrṇakeyūrābaddhabāhavaḥ|
mayūrabarhasaṃkāśacārukuñcitamūrdhajāḥ|| 129.37||
kalpadrumasamudbhūtakusumasragvibhūṣaṇāḥ|
śukāṅgaharitākārakañcukottaṃsitastanāḥ|| 129.38||
mattamātaṅgavikrāntalīlāvibhramarecakāḥ|
mattakokiladātyūhakalanisvanabhāṣitāḥ|| 129.39||
mahatām apyupāttānāṃ tapasāṃ vighnahetavaḥ|
darśayāmāsurātmānaṃ vidviṣāṃ vadhahetavaḥ|| 129.40||
atha te 'apsaraso dṛṣṭvā daiteyāḥ kāmamohitāḥ|
tāsām arthe varāṅgīnām abhijaghnuḥ parasparam|| 129.41||
gadāparighacakrāsiśūlamudgaraśaktibhiḥ|
dhanuḥkuliśatīkṣṇāgrabhindipālaparaśvadhaiḥ|| 129.42||
mameyaṃ cārusarvāṅgī na taveyaṃ sumadhyamā|
athavā yuddhaśulkāstu muñcaināṃ praharasva mām|| 129.43||
ityuktvā vividhā vāco daiteyāḥ kālacoditāḥ|
anyonyavadham āsādya prajagmuste yamakṣayam|| 129.44||
hataśiṣṭāstu ye tatra dānavāḥ śāntapauruṣāḥ|
vibudhairugratejobhiste 'api sarve raṇe hatāḥ|| 129.45||
ya idaṃ paṭhate viśuddhabuddhirnidhanaṃ saṃsadi dānaveśvarāṇām|
manujo yuvatīrihaiva loke sa labhedapsarasāṃ samānarūpāḥ|| 129.46||
iti skandapurāṇe andhakārayuddhe ūnatriṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 129.129||

skandapurana130
vyāsa uvāca|
andhakaḥ sa kathaṃ daityo hareṇa vinipātitaḥ|
yasya trailokyam akhilaṃ bhayāt sarvaṃ vaśe sthitam|| 130.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
andhako nāma daityendra ādau trailokyakaṇṭakaḥ|
brahmaṇastu varān prāpya so 'avadhyo devamānuṣaiḥ|| 130.2||
na tasya yuddhe kruddhasya viṣṇuḥ śakro yamo 'atha vā|
śakto hyabhimukhe sthātuṃ kim utānye divaukasaḥ|| 130.3||
sa kadācidbalodvṛttaḥ paryaṭan pṛthivīm imām|
apaśyanmandaraprasthe devīṃ himavataḥ sutām|| 130.4||
sa tām ālokya daityendraḥ kāmopahatacetanaḥ|
aham eva prabhuriti devyāṃ dauṣṭyam acintayat|| 130.5||
cintayitvā tu tāṃ prāha dānavānanuyāyinaḥ|
ānyadhvam imāṃ śīghraṃ matsamīpaṃ nagātmajamām|| 130.6||
tacchrutvā tasya vacanaṃ manmathāviṣṭacetasaḥ|
prahlādo vadatāṃ śreṣṭha idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 130.7||
dānavendra hitaṃ vākyaṃ yadāyatyāṃ viśudhyate|
avaśyaṃ tanmayā vācyaṃ bandhusnehādviśeṣataḥ|| 130.8||
eṣā himavataḥ putrī patnī śarvasya dhīmataḥ|
nāsyāṃ dauṣṭyaṃ tvayā cintyaṃ mā nas dhakṣyati tejasā|| 130.9||
jagato mātaraṃ devīṃ pūjyāṃ duṣprekṣyatejasam|
umāṃ dānavaśārdūla nādhikṣeptum ihārhasi|| 130.10||
kiṃ kaṇṭhe mahatīṃ baddhvā śilāṃ mūḍhena cetasā|
gambhīrāvartinīṃ bhīmāṃ nadīṃ tvaṃ tartum icchasi|| 130.11||
bhūtvā pataṅgaḥ kiṃ mohācchikhāṃ dīptāṃ vibhāvasoḥ|
dānavānām adhipate nāśāya spraṣṭum icchasi|| 130.12||
mā vināśaṃ nayeḥ sarvān samūlān dānaveśvara|
nivartyatāṃ mano devyā naitadyuktaṃ vipaścitām|| 130.13||
tvaṃ vipaścit kulīnaśca kulīnānāṃ ca gotrajaḥ|
yajvā ca dharmanityaśca naitadyuktaṃ tava prabho|| 130.14||
tava santi striyo bahvyaḥ sarvāśca sthirayauvanāḥ|
prakṛtyaiva surūpāṅgyo devyāśceto nivartyatām|| 130.15||
yo 'asmākaṃ tapasā tuṣṭo yacchate kāṅkṣitān varān|
tasya tvaṃ devadevasya devyāḥ pāpaṃ cikīrṣasi|| 130.16||
yena dakṣaḥ kratuḥ kālaḥ kāmaśca gamitaḥ kṣayam|
tasya tvaṃ devadevasya dehārdhaṃ hartum icchasi|| 130.17||
liṅgeṣu yo 'arcyate devaḥ surāsuramahoragaiḥ|
tasya devīṃ jagaddhātrīṃ kathaṃ tvam avamanyase|| 130.18||
sa caiko nābhimantavyastvayā devaḥ pinākadhṛk|
icchan kuryāddhi rūpāṇāṃ sashasrāṇi śatāni ca|| 130.19||
pramathānāṃ sahasrāṇi yogināṃ bhīmakarmaṇām|
tasyāgrato vrajantyete yathaiva tava dānavāḥ|| 130.20||
yo haredbhāskarāddīptiṃ candrāt kāntiṃ kṣiteḥ kṣamām|
vāsukeryo hareddaṃṣṭrāṃ sa haret tasya pārvatīm|| 130.21||
tasyottamāṅgaṃ sakalaṃ śatadhā śakalībhavet|
yaḥ śarvabhāryāṃ tām āryām avamanyeta bāliśaḥ|| 130.22||
pitāmahena yaccoktastadā tvaṃ padmayoninā|
varadānāvasāne tu vacastat smartum arhasi|| 130.23||
yaiṣā śrīste ditisuta mayā dattā sudurlabhā|
durnayena tavaiveyaṃ yāsyatyanyatra danāva|| 130.24||
kaṭukānyapi pathyāni bandhūnāṃ vacanāni ye|
na śṛṇvantyanayopetāste yānti nidhanaṃ narāḥ|| 130.25||
sameṣyāma vayaṃ devaṃ priyārthe tava śaṃkaram|
sametyānusameṣyāmaḥ sarve vaivasvatakṣaye|| 130.26||
ityuktaḥ sa tadā tena bandhunā śobhanaṃ vacaḥ|
naitadevam iti prāha prahasan kālacoditaḥ|| 130.27||
tasminnaprihārye tu kāryākārye priye mama|
yadi yuddhe kṣayo me syāt kṣayo 'api vijayo mama|| 130.28||
manasaiva hi bhūtānāṃ vidadhānaḥ śubhāśubham|
tathā vāpyanyathā vāpi kāla eva kariṣyati|| 130.29||
pratyākhyāya tato rāgāt prahlādaṃ dānaveśvaraḥ|
devīṃ spraṣṭuṃ dadhe cetaḥ pataṅgo 'agniśikhām iva|| 130.30||
atha buddhvā bhagavatī duṣṭabhāvaṃ durātmanaḥ|
gaṇān ājñāpayāmāsa yuddhāya sumahābalān|| 130.31||
atha te jñāpitā devyā vividhāyudhapāṇayaḥ|
dānavābhimukhībhūtāḥ somanandipuraḥsarāḥ|| 130.32||
te kṛtvā sumahadyuddhaṃ dānavānucaraiḥ saha|
vikṣiptā dānavendreṇa vāyunā jaladā iva|| 130.33||
etasminnantare devī dṛṣṭvodīrṇaṃ tam andhakam|
svayam evābhidudrāva gṛhītvā saśaraṃ dhanuḥ|| 130.34||
andhakaṃ pañcaviṃśatyā sā jaghāna stanāntare|
śarāṇāṃ niśitāgrāṇāṃ sa mumoha papāta ca|| 130.35||
sa muhūrtāt tadā saṃjñāṃ labdhvā mānācca dānavaḥ|
uttasthau vegavāñchīghram ugrodyataśarāsanaḥ|| 130.36||
tataḥ sa utthāya punardevīṃ prati mahāsuraḥ|
mumoca śaravarṣāṇi varṣāṇīva balāhakaḥ|| 130.37||
tatastriśūlam udyamya devīṃ dīptāgnitejasam|
andhakaṃ hantum ārabdhāṃ śanairdevo nyaṣedhayat|| 130.38||
dānavendro mamaivāyaṃ śāsyo mā tvaṃ śramaṃ kṛthāḥ|
aham evāsya śūlena bhetsyāmi hṛdayaṃ raṇe|| 130.39||
evam uktā tu sā devī devadevena pārvatī|
virarāma tato yuddhādadṛśyā sambabhūva ca|| 130.40||
tato devaḥ svayaṃ prāha nandinaṃ gaṇanāyakam|
yudhyadhvaṃ dānavaiḥ sārdhaṃ gaṇān āhūya sarvaśaḥ|| 130.41||
āhūya nandī tān sarvān gaṇāñcharvājñayā tadā|
uvāca bhūyo deveśaṃ śṛṇu ye 'abhyāgatā gaṇāḥ|| 130.42||
viśiṣṭeṣṭāstvayā sṛṣṭāḥ svayaṃ sṛṣṭau sanātanāḥ|
prajābhāvena nānātvaṃ yeṣāṃ tattvaṃ sudurvacam|| 130.43||
vṛṣadhvajā vṛṣarathāścandrāvayavabhūṣaṇāḥ|
ta ime samanuprāptā rurdrā rudra tava priyāḥ|| 130.44||
koṭīśatasahasrāṇāṃ śatam eṣāṃ mahātmanām|
tāvanti ca sahasrāṇi śatāni ca tathā vibho|| 130.45||
ṣaṣṭiścaiva sahasrāṇi yeṣāṃ tulyo na vidyate|
devānāṃ nīlakaṇṭhānāṃ nīlakaṇṭhamahātmanām|| 130.46||
ete śurā baleṣūgrā ugrodagraparākramāḥ|
yudhyamānāḥ kariṣyanti tava pramuditaṃ manaḥ|| 130.47||
eteṣām eva rudrāṇām anurūpāḥ prabhāvataḥ|
tanmātrā dvārapālā vai vikrāntāḥ krāntamanyavaḥ|| 130.48||
itīme kapisiṃhāsyāḥ kapisiṃhabalā raṇe|
dānavaiḥ saha yotsyanti vāraṇā iva vāraṇaiḥ|| 130.49||
rudrāśca rudraputrāśca rudrāṇāṃ ye ca pārṣadāḥ|
rudrādhipa na kiṃciddhi yeṣāṃ sādhyaṃ na vidyate|| 130.50||
ekaikasyāsya rudrasya putrāḥ putravatāṃ vara|
pañca pañca mahāvīryāḥ kākapakṣadharāśca te|| 130.51||
bhujataḥ sahasotpannāstava ye krodhasambhavāḥ|
vīrabhadraṃ puraskṛtya ta ime samupathitāḥ|| 130.52||
eṣāṃ ṣaṣṭiḥ smṛtāḥ koṭyaḥ sahasrāṇi ca ṣoḍaśa|
gaṇapānāṃ gaṇādhyakṣa tvatpriyāṇām ihāgatāḥ|| 130.53||
evaṃ deva priyārthaṃ te dakṣayajñaḥ samṛddhimān|
yairdhvastaḥ purahan deva paśya tān punarāgatān|| 130.54||
āpadbhāvaprapannāstu yena khyātāstvayānagha|
koṭīśatasahasrākhyāste 'apyamī samupasthitāḥ|| 130.56||
mahānalā yathā vṛkṣān pradīptān vāyunā saha|
ete 'abhinirdahiṣyanti dānavāṃstvatpriye ratāḥ|| 130.57||
guhāvāsa guhyasyāpi krīḍamānasya ye suraiḥ|
priyārthaṃ gaṇapā dattā nānāmṛgaśatānanāḥ|| 130.58||
jvalanācalavat teṣāṃ triṃśatkoṭyo maheśvara|
gaṇapānām anuprāptāḥ priyaṃ kartuṃ tavānagha|| 130.59||
ime raktambaradharā raktasraganulepanāḥ|
oṣṭhajādrudhirājjātā raktā nāma gaṇeśvarāḥ|| 130.60||
aṅgārakasyānucarā mahābalaparākramāḥ|
ṣaṣṭikoṭisahasrāṇi ta ime samupasthitāḥ|| 130.61||
mantavyaṃ na balaṃ cāpi etanmātraṃ tvayānagha|
ete hyaṣṭaguṇaiśvaryaṃ tava deva prasādajam|| 130.62||
sambibhrāṇā maheśāna kariṣyanti bahūnapi|
lokānete samudyuktān sadevāsuramānuṣān|| 130.63||
saṃyuge yugamūlāntaṃ daheyuḥ suradānavān|
ya ete kundasaṃkāśāḥ svarṇotpalavibhūṣitāḥ|| 130.64||
daṃśitā gaṇepeśāna sarve yuddhakutūhalāḥ|
brahmaṇyāsta ime śūrāścandrāvayavabhūṣaṇāḥ|| 130.65||
rudrā rudrapate prāptāḥ paśyemān yuddhalālasān|
bālārkasamavarṇābhāḥ saśastrāśca caturbhujāḥ|| 130.66||
dvārapālā hyamī deva kapīndrasadṛśānanāḥ|
raktāmbarā raktamālyā raktacandanarūṣitāḥ|| 130.67||
brahmaṇyā varadāḥ śūrāḥ kaumārabrahmacāriṇaḥ|
mattabarhisamārūḍhāḥ sarve vai śaktipāṇayaḥ|| 130.68||
ete vikrāntavikrāntāḥ skandā nāma kumārakāḥ|
uccaiḥśravaḥpratisamānaśvān ye hemamālinaḥ|| 130.69||
virejurāsthitā deva pītakauśeyavāsasaḥ|
bālārkasamavarṇābhā bālotpaladalekṣaṇāḥ|| 130.70||
viśākhā nāma te putrā rudrāṇāṃ śaktipāṇayaḥ|
yānetān īkṣase deva sitavastrān sitānanān|| 130.71||
vidyotamānān vapuṣā bahūṃścandrānivoditān|
kākapakṣadharān muṇḍāṃstāmracūḍeśvavasthitān|| 130.72||
ete vikhyātavīryāste śākhā nāma kumārakāḥ|
ya ime chāgameṣasthāḥ kiṃśukāśokavarcasaḥ|| 130.73||
śūrāścaudāryavantaśca śiśutāmarasānanāḥ|
naigameṣasya putrasya tava tulyaparicchadāḥ|| 130.74||
naigameṣā iti khyātā hyete deva kumārakāḥ|
ya ime kālameghābhāḥ kālameghanibhasvanāḥ|| 130.75||
keśajāstava te deva pramathāḥ samupasthitāḥ|
ime ca raktā bahavo gaṇāḥ parabalārdanāḥ|| 130.76||
barūthino varmiṇaśca rathinaścitrayodhinaḥ|
nānāpraharaṇāḥ sarve sarve yuddhaviśāradāḥ|| 130.77||
kṛtino yuddhaśauṇḍāśca sarva eva ca daṃśitāḥ|
sitāsitānāṃ meghānāṃ girīṇāṃ ca samatviṣaḥ|
sanakramīnamakarā ye samudrā ivoddhatāḥ|| 130.78||
siṃhavyāghravarāhāsyāḥ parighāśanipāṇayaḥ|
tavaivānugrahādete pramathāstvām upasthitāḥ|| 130.79||
ete vai pārṣadāḥ śūrāḥ skandasya paramātmanaḥ|
tridaśaiḥ krīḍanaṃ dattāḥ sarvaśastvām upasthitāḥ|| 130.80||
dṛptapramuditaṃ sphītaṃ pramathānīkam īśvara|
dānavānīkabhedārthe samartham iti me matiḥ|| 130.81||
pravihāyānyakāryāṇi paramādaram āsthitam|
devārīṇām anarthāya vidhvaṃsayadanantaram (?)|| 130.82||
karigiritarutoraṇaprabhāstaruṇadivākaratulyatejasaḥ|
gaṇapatipatayastava hyamī ripubalam īśvara jetum udyatāḥ|| 130.83||
acaracarapate tato 'andhakaḥ pratisamatāṃ labhate raṇe sthitaḥ|
gaṇapatiśatayūthasaṃvṛtto visṛja vibho 'avanatān gaṇeśvarān|| 130.84||
iti skandapurāṇe andhakayuddhopakrame triṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 130.130||

skandapurana131
sanatkumāra uvāca|
athāpaśyat tadāyātān bhagavān gaṇanāyakān|
svairanīkaiḥ subahuśaḥ saṃnaddhān yuddhalālasān|| 131.1||
diṇḍiṃ ca bhārabhūtiṃ ca somaśarmāṇam eva ca|
karikaṃ meghanādaṃ ca udaremaṇim eva ca|| 131.2||
āsattiṃ dhūtapāpaṃ ca candramaulinam eva ca|
ādityamālaṃ vikrāntaṃ sukeśaṃ ca mahābalam|| 131.3||
tālaketuṃ jvaraṃ caiva daṇḍapāṇim ūrjitam|
etāṃścānyāṃśca vikhyātān guhyāṃśca gaṇanāyakān|| 131.4||
mahāgaṇapatiṃ caiva khoṭhāmudgaram eva ca|
sampūjya bhagavān sarvān prasādya ca punaḥ punaḥ|| 131.5||
uvāca meghanirhrādaḥ śatadundubhinisvanaḥ|
dānavaiḥ saha yūyaṃ me yoddhum arhatha sattamāḥ|| 131.6||
yūyam eva gaṇādhyakṣāḥ paryāptāstān prabādhane|
tasmādyūyaṃ mahāsattvāḥ sagaṇāḥ sapadānugāḥ|
gacchadhvaṃ saṃvināśāya pūjito 'asmi mahābalāḥ|| 131.7||
ta evam uktā devena praṇamya śirasā haram|
viprajagmurmahātmāno devo 'api sampratiṣṭhata|| 131.8||
tataḥ samabhavacchabda udadheriva bhidyataḥ|
andhakāsurasainyasya mandaraṃ samupeyuṣaḥ|| 131.9||
niśāmya dānavārāvaṃ śrotrāyāsakaraṃ bhṛśam|
pramathā rurudhurghoraṃ yugānte jaladā iva|| 131.10||
tāvanyonyabaloddhūtāvabhūtāṃ sainyasāgarau|
pralayānta ivoddhūtau bhidyamānau mahārṇavau|| 131.11||
devadeva uvāca|
juhudhyarivināśāya brahmannasmajjayāya ca|
tvaṃ cāpi nandin rakṣasva sarvairetairgaṇairvṛtaḥ|| 131.12||
ākāśasthāśca ye hyete nadantyambumuco yathā|
ākāśagāneva ripūnete bādhantu dānavān|| 131.13||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ityuktau tau prārabhetāṃ kartuṃ bhagavato vacaḥ|
bṛhaspatirjuhāvāgniṃ nandī cāpi rarakṣa tam|| 131.14||
vyāyacchadbhirmahadbhiśca pramathirmandaro giriḥ|
viprasthita ivābhāti srastakuñjarakesariḥ|| 131.15||
tato 'andhakabala dṛptaṃ siṃhabalaṃ yathā|
ārohamāṇaṃ tat tūrṇaṃ cālayat tam ivācalam|| 131.16||
tato halahalāśabdaḥ pramathānām ajāyata|
daityān vāryatāṃ yuddhe tarupāṣāṇasāyakaiḥ|| 131.17||
dānavā vāryamāṇāstu pramathirjitakāśibhiḥ|
vidārya pramathānīkaṃ śīghram āruruhustadā|| 131.18||
pramathā hyapi nissaṅgaṃ yoddhavyam iti niścitāḥ|
cicchidurbibhiduścaiva paphaluśca suretarān|| 131.19||
gṛhṇīṣva muñca tiṣṭheti sthitastvaṃ kiṃ kariṣyasi|
evaṃvācaḥ samuttasthuḥ pramathāsurasainyayoḥ|| 131.20||
samūlāgraistaruvaraiḥ parvataiśca sapādapaiḥ|
anyonyaṃ cūrṇayanti sma nirghṛṇāḥ pramathāsurāḥ|| 131.21||
tato dākṣāyaṇīputrairdakṣādhvaravināśanāḥ|
parāṅmukhā na śakitāḥ kartuṃ bhaktyaparāṅmukhāḥ|| 131.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
arohaṇe 'acalāgrasya aśaktān nirjitān ripūn|
devopalabhya pramathānavārayadaśeṣataḥ|| 131.23||
devadeva uvāca|
ārohantu danoḥ putrā mandaraṃ cārukandaram|
krīḍārthaṃ mama yudhyadhvam ebhiḥ saha gaṇādhipāḥ|| 131.24||
atha dadṛśuranekacārukuñjasthitamṛgarājavimuktabhīmanādam|
prasṛtagajakulābhighātarugṇakṣitiruhapuṣpasamācitapradeśam|| 131.25||
bhujagapatiśiromaṇipradīpapratihatacāruśilāgṛhāndhakāram|
śiśiravimalanirjharāmbuvegasphuṭitamahopalajāladṛṣṭarandhram|| 131.26||
kvacidabhinavatāmrapallavāgrapratihatabāladivākarāṃśujālam|
kvacidamaravilāsinīmukhendupraviracitasphuṭacārupatralekham|| 131.27||
kvacidanilavidhūtacārupuṣpastabakavicitritakānanapradeśam|
sphaṭikamaṇiśilātalopaviṣṭasthitakapiyūthavilokitātmadeham|| 131.28||
surayuvatiniketabarhikekāśravaṇasukhapratibuddhasiddhasārtham|
kamaladalarajaḥsugandhitoyasthitakalahaṃsakalapralāparamyam|| 131.29||
dinakarakarataptasūryakāntapravigalitāgnivilīnahemadhātum|
kvacidabhipatitāṃśucandrakāntapravisṛtaśailanadīvikīrṇatoyam|| 131.30||
varaharikaravajrasaṃnipātasphuṭitamahāgajakumbhamauktikaughaiḥ|
sitakusumacayairiva prakīrṇaiḥ kvacidupaśobhitavistṛtopakaṇṭham|| 131.31||
pramuditagaṇabhairavāṭṭahāsaprasṛtamahāravapūritāntarālam|
tarugahanalatāgṛhāntalīnapramuditasiddhavadhūpranṛttaramyam|| 131.32||
bahukaṭakavicārimattanāgaṃ bahumṛgaśāvanipītanirjharāmbum|
bahuviṣamataṭaprapātakuñjaṃ bahuvidhagulmalatāvatānavṛkṣam|| 131.34||
marakatamaṇipadmarāgaśṛṅgadyutiśabalīkṛtapādapādapāgryam|
alikulakalakokilāvinādapracuravināditacārukānanāntam|| 131.34||
yasmin sadā pramuditā jitamṛtyuśokā gorocanāñjanaśilālanidhānasiddhāḥ|
siddhāḥ sadā pramuditā vanitāsahāyāstiṣṭhanti candrakiraṇopamacāruhārāḥ|| 131.35||
vidyādharāḥ priyatamāvinibaddharāgāḥ pīneṣu tuṅgataṭavatsu payodhareṣu|
dhātūtkarairharitaraktapiśaṅgavarṇairyatrālikhanti vividhān kusumāvataṃsān|| 131.36||
yasmin sadā suratakheditagātrayaṣṭyaḥ kāntāgrahastaviniveśitahastapadmāḥ|
sevanti nirjharajalapraṇayātiśītam abhyāgataṃ pavanam apasaraso 'atihṛṣṭāḥ|| 131.37||
nūpurarāvibodhitahaṃsaṃ haṃsatanūruhaghaṭṭitapadmam|
padmarajoruṇitāmalatoyaṃ toyapariṣkṛtakāñcanaśṛṅgam|| 131.38||
śṛṅgasamutthitacandanavṛkṣaṃ vṛkṣasamāsthitakokilavṛndam|
vṛndavimuktagajendraninādaṃ nādabhayākulitarkṣatarakṣum|| 131.39||
ṛkṣatarakṣunilīnanikuñjaṃ kuñjaguhāmukhanirgatasiṃham|
siṃhavidāritanaikapakumbhaṃ kumbhavinirgatamauktikaratnam|| 131.40||
ratnamayūkhavibhāsitapṛṣṭhaṃ pṛṣṭhasamāsthitaśaṃkarapādam|
pādasamutthitapādapaṣaṇḍaṃ ṣaṇḍalatākusumotkaramārgam|| 131.41||
mārgamārgamaṇitoraṇacitraṃ citracitramaṇitoraṇapaṭṭam|
paṭṭapaṭṭaviniveśitapuṣpaṃ puṣpapuṣpaparicumbitabhṛṅgam|| 131.42||
nānādhātuvicitranitambaṃ nānāpuṣpalatāgṛharamyam|
nānāmattavihaṃgamaghuṣṭaṃ nānāśṛṅgasamāsthitasiddham|| 131.43||
tanmandaraṃ vividhacāraṇasiddhasaṃghai ramyaṃ svayaṃ trinayanena kṛtādhivāsam|
daityāstadā bhagavatānumatapraveśāḥ sarve samāruruhurātmajayaiṣiṇaste|| 131.44||
tato visṛṣṭāḥ pramathairārohanta diteḥ sutāḥ|
manvānāḥ pramathā bhītā nivṛttā iti satvaram|| 131.45||
mandarasya tataḥ pṛṣṭhe nānādrumasamākule|
baddhaskandhāḥ sthitā daityā ādityasadṛśaprabhāḥ|| 131.46||
sa mandaro bhīmaśilopaladrumo vivṛddhaśārdūlatarakṣuvāraṇaḥ|
mahāsurairdarpitavājivāraṇairvikīryate megha ivānilairbhṛśam|| 131.47||
kṣipanti śubhrābhranibhāḥ śilāḥ kvacit tarūn samutpāṭya nadanti meghavat|
nivāryamāṇāḥ pramathān samārdayan vaneṣu siṃhā mṛgayūthapāniva|| 131.48||
tatastu tadgajarathavājidānavaiḥ samāvṛtaṃ kṣubhitamahodadhiprabham|
virājate ditisutabāhupālitaṃ vanaṃ yathā mṛgapatibāhupālitam|| 131.49||
iti skandapurāṇe andhakayuddhopakrame mandaravarṇanaṃ nāma
ekatriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 131.131||

skandapurana132
sanatkumāra uvāca|
mandaraprastham āsādya so 'andhako dānavādhipaḥ|
prāñjaliḥ śukram āhedaṃ śakrārkasadṛśādyutim|| 132.1||
andhaka uvāca|
prāptāḥ sma bhagavañchailaṃ mandaraṃ cārukandaram|
pramathairbhīmasaṃkāśaiḥ saṃniruddhaśilātalam|| 132.2||
khecarā māyinaścaiva yoginaśca mahābalāḥ|
prasabhaṃ dānavairjetuṃ na śakyā gaṇanāyakāḥ|| 132.3||
prāyeṇa balavanto 'api hyupāyenaiva sādhavaḥ|
kāryeṣu ādau pravartante paścāt tu viparītavat|| 132.4||
tadupāyaṃ samāsthāya viśeṣeṇa samāhitāḥ|
pramathān saṃprabādhāma yathā vā rucitaṃ tava|| 132.5||
sa tvam asmajjayaprepsurdānavānāṃ jayāya ca|
kuru deva girivyūhaṃ paravyūhavidāraṇam|| 132.6||
ke ceme sūryakoṭīnāṃ prabhāvarṇavapurdharāḥ|
pramathānīkamadhyeṣu sthitāḥ paśyanti māṃ muhuḥ|| 132.7||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato 'andhakavacaḥ śrutvā kruddho daityapurohitaḥ|
uvāca daityādhipatiṃ gopatiṃ darśayanniva|| 132.8||
śukra uvāca|
ya eṣa madhupiṅgākṣastryambakaścandrabhūṣaṇaḥ|
vyāghracarmāmbaradharo deva eṣa pinākadhṛk|| 132.9||
yastveṣa kapisiṃhāsyo nīlavastraścaturbhujaḥ|
taruṇārkasamo bhāti nandyeṣa gaṇanāyakaḥ|| 132.10||
tanurucco 'agnisaṃkāśo ya eṣo 'agnirivojjvalaḥ|
brāhmaṇādhipatirhyeṣa bṛhadbuddhirbṛhaspatiḥ|| 132.11||
ya eṣa nātidūrastho vṛṣaketostriśūladhṛk|
eṣo 'andhako mahākāyo mahāgaṇapatirvaraḥ|| 132.12||
ya eṣa āsthāya kūjantaṃ bhāti citrakalāpinam|
mayūraṃ bālasūryābhaḥ śaktipāṇirmahābalaḥ|| 132.13||
brahmaṇyo brahmanirato brahmacārī yatavrataḥ|
skanda eṣa hi devānām agraṇīrdānavā raṇe|| 132.14||
ya eṣa tāmracūḍasthastāmracūḍaśilāprabhaḥ|
śaktim ullolayan bhāti toyadastaḍitaṃ yathā|| 132.15||
kākapakṣadharo hyeṣa pūrṇacandranibhānanaḥ|
viśākho nāma kaumāraḥ kaumārabrahmacaryavān|| 132.16||
taruṇastaruṇaprajñastaruḥ śākhāyuto yathā|
svāhāyāstanayo hyeṣa śākho nāma mahādyutiḥ|| 132.17||
etasya yo hyasau pārśvaṃ savyam āvṛtya tiṣṭhati|
darśayānaḥ pradeśinyā māṃ ca tvāṃ ca punaḥ punaḥ|| 132.18||
meṣam āsthāya balavān bāla eva vyavasthitaḥ|
naigameṣa iti khyāta eṣo 'andhaka harātmajaḥ|| 132.19||
caturbhireṣa putraistu dṛśyate 'asurahā vṛtaḥ|
devaiścaturbhiḥ sampṛkto yathaiva hi pitāmahaḥ|| 132.20||
devam īśaṃ maheṣvāsaṃ nandisūnupuraḥsaram|
vyatiyudhyāsuraśreṣṭha manmantraparipālitaḥ|| 132.21||
pramathairnihatān daityān śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|
aham utthāpayiṣyāmi śasyāni jalado yathā|| 132.22||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
taṃ bhārgava iti procya dānavān dānavādhipam|
girivyūhena tat sainyaṃ prākramadvyūhituṃ tataḥ|| 132.23||
mūle 'andhakarathaṃ kṛtvā sāndhakaṃ sāśvasārathim|
pādātairbahusāhasraiḥ pādāṃstasya cakāra ha|| 132.24||
teṣu pādasahasreṣu girivyūhasya dānavaiḥ|
vṛkṣaśailaśilāsaṃghān kārayamāsa bhārgavaḥ|| 132.25||
koṭibhirdaśabhistasya dānavānāṃ mahātmanām|
nitambāṃstāmranayanān pracakāra graheśvaraḥ|| 132.26||
dhātuniṣyandacitreṣu nitambeṣvapi dānavān|
tṛṇavat kṣupavaccāpi sthāpayāmāsa bhārgavaḥ|| 132.27||
triṃśatā koṭibhiścāpi tridaśādhipavidviṣām|
girivyūhasya śṛṅgāni cakārārkasamaprabhaḥ|| 132.28||
teṣu śṛṅgeṣu tuṅgeṣu dānavān sāyudhānatha|
amī prapātā ityevam ācakhyau bhṛgunandanaḥ|| 132.29||
te prapātasthitā daityā nīlāmbudharavarcasaḥ|
śastratoyāni muditāḥ kṣaranta iva saṃsthitāḥ|| 132.30||
balasthā ye javopetā daityā daivatakaṇṭhakāḥ|
śyenavat te bhramitvā tu nilīnāḥ syurgirivraje|| 132.31||
nivātakavacān sarvān vividhāyudhadhāriṇaḥ|
akarodbhārgavo devo girivyūhasya sānuvat|| 132.32||
prahlādam atha saṃhrādam anuhrādaṃ śiniṃ tathā|
jambhaṃ kujambhaṃ tāraṃ ca mayaṃ namucim eva ca|| 132.33||
virocanaṃ baliṃ bāṇaṃ vātaṃ kārtasvanaṃ kuśam|
śambhuṃ ca bhāvayatyaṃ ca ilvakaṃ bilvakaṃ tathā|| 132.34||
vitaṃ vṛttaṃ tuhuṇḍaṃ ca huṇḍaṃ daṇḍaṃ ca dānavam|
añjanaṃ ruṣaṇaṃ rāhuṃ svarbhānum ajakaṃ gajam|| 132.35||
hastiduryodhanau caiva pākaṃ dhundhuṃ ca dānavam|
etāṃścānyāṃśca balino daityān daivatakaṇṭakān|| 132.36||
vyūhaṃ rakṣata yudhyadhvam ityuvācāsurādhipaḥ|
himavāniva śailendro vindhyo vādbhutagahvaraḥ|| 132.37||
sa girivyūha ābhāti śastrakaṇṭakitadrumaḥ|
andhakāram ivaikasthaṃ meghānām iva saṃcayam|| 132.38||
dṛṣṭvā dṛṣṭvā girivyūhaṃ pramathā vismayaṃ yayuḥ|
parvatavyūham ālokya parvatavyūhasaṃsthitāḥ|| 132.39||
neduste 'asuraśārdūlā meghā lokātyaye yathā|
ūcuśca na hi śakyo 'ayaṃ bhettuṃ devaiḥ savāsavaiḥ|| 132.40||
pramathāḥ kiṃ kariṣyanti svalpavīryaparākramāḥ|
jīvayiṣyati naḥ śukro mṛtānapi na saṃśayaḥ|
yudhyadhvaṃ dānavaśreṣṭhā niśśaṅkairantarātmabhiḥ|| 132.41||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
girivyūhaṃ tato dṛṣṭvā bhārgavottamanirmitam|
devaḥ kapardī prāhedaṃ bṛhadbuddhiṃ bṛhaspatim|| 132.42||
vācaspate girivyūhaṃ paśya śukreṇa nirmitam|
śṛṅgavantaṃ darīvantaṃ himavantaṃ yathā girim|| 132.43||
lokān sajalapātālān saviṣṇūn sapitāmahān|
grasedeṣa girivyūha upekṣā kriyate yadi|| 132.44||
nainaṃ devā na gandharvā na nāgā na nagāstathā|
śaknuyurbhettum udyuktā vinaitān gaṇanāyakān|| 132.45||
girivyūhasya viprendra nānyaṃ paśyāmi bhedanam|
vajravyūham ṛte dhīman sarvavyūhabhidaṃ mahat|| 132.46||
sa tvaṃ brahmavidāṃ śreṣṭha girivyūhavidāraṇam|
vajravyūhaṃ kuruṣvādya pramathāyutasaṃvṛtam|| 132.47||
śambhunā caivam uktastu brāhmaṇendro bṛhaspatiḥ|
vajravyūhena taṃ vyūhaṃ pratyavyūhat tadā navam|| 132.48||
bāhujān bahusahasrān bhaktāṃścaiva gaṇādhipān|
vajravyūhasya madhye vai sthāpayāmāsa buddhimān|| 132.49||
skandasya pārṣadaiḥ śūraiḥ surāsuranighātibhiḥ|
sahasraṃ parvaṇāṃ tasya vajravyūhasya nirmamau|| 132.50||
koṭiṃ koṭipravīrāṇāṃ pramathānāṃ prahāriṇām|
vajradhārāsu sarvāsu sthāpayāmāsa sa dvijaḥ|| 132.51||
kumāraṃ ca viśākhaṃ ca śākhaṃ chāgamukhaṃ tathā|
cakāra so 'aṅgirā devo vajravyūhasya kuḍmalam|| 132.52||
kuḍmalāgre caturbāhuḥ kapīndravadano 'arihā|
sthito vajrodyatakaro nandī dinakaraprabhaḥ|| 132.53||
kuṇḍodaraṃ nandiṣeṇaṃ ghaṇṭākarṇaṃ mahodaram|
paścārdhe tasya vajrasya kuḍmalaṃ saṃnyaveśayat|| 132.54||
somanandī tu tasyāgre vyāghravaktro gaṇeśvaraḥ|
sārkacandrāyutaprakhyaḥ sthito vai paṭṭiśāyudhaḥ|| 132.55||
rudrāṇāṃ dvārapālāśca rudrā rudrasutāśca ye|
itaścetaśca vinyastā vajravyūhābhirakṣiṇaḥ|| 132.56||
vajravyūhasya madhye tu rathavarye pratiṣṭhitaḥ|
tasthau īśo bhavaḥ śarvaḥ kapardī nīlalohitaḥ|| 132.57||
tasya keturmahāñchveto vibhātīndradhvajopamaḥ|
mandaraścandrabimbena juṣṭaśṛṅga ivācalaḥ|| 132.58||
śatadhāro naikaparvā cāruśobhitakuḍmalaḥ|
vajravyūho girivyūhaṃ bhettukāma ivābhavat|| 132.59||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā nirmitaṃ vyūhaṃ devagandharvaguhyakāḥ|
sādhu sādhviti vai nedurvismayotphullalocanāḥ|| 132.60||
atha gaṇapabaleṣu siṃhanādāḥ paṇavamṛdaṅgamaśaṅkhanādamiśrāḥ|
dititanayabhayapradāḥ pravṛttāḥ kṣubhitasamudrapayodanādakalpāḥ|| 132.61||
iti skandapurāṇe andhakamathane vyūharacanā nāma
dvātriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 132.132||

skandapurana133
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tau dṛṣṭvā nirmitau vyūhau pramathāsurayoḥ surāḥ|
vimānakoṭibhiḥ śīghraṃ rurudhuḥ sarvato nabhaḥ|| 133.1||
sarvaṃ tejobhirākīrṇaṃ tadambaratalaṃ babhau|
merukūṭavanaṃ ramyaṃ dahyamānam ivāgninā|| 133.2||
devadundubhiśabdāḍhyaṃ divyastrīśatasaṃkulam|
taddevamaṇḍalaṃ bhāti yathaivādityamaṇḍalam|| 133.3||
divyapuṣpasamākīrṇaṃ divyagandhādhivāsitam|
prekṣakaiḥ śataśaḥ pūrṇaṃ khatalaṃ divyam ābabhau|| 133.4||
vāditrāṇyabhyahanyanta jaguśca suragāyanāḥ|
rambhādyā nanṛtuścāpi śubhāpāṅgāḥ surāṅganāḥ|| 133.5||
atha vajragirivyūhau parasparajayaiṣiṇau|
samīyaturmahānādairvātoddhūtau yathārṇavau|| 133.6||
mā tvaradhvam iti proktāḥ śukreṇa sumahātmanā|
yodhā nivāryamāṇāpi cakruryuddham asaṃhatam|| 133.7||
tataḥ śaṅkhāśca bheryaśca paṇavā goviṣāṇakāḥ|
āḍambarā ḍiṇḍimāśca maṇḍūkāḥ paṇavā hyapi|| 133.8||
bheryo dundubhayaścāpi mṛdaṅgāḥ kiṃkharānakāḥ|
ubhayatra bale gāḍhaṃ prāvādyanta sahasraśaḥ|| 133.9||
tataḥ suragaṇairnādāḥ saha gandharvacāraṇaiḥ|
kṛtāstūryaravaṃ śrutvā pramathāsurasainyayoḥ|| 133.10||
balayostūryaśabdena devasiṃharaveṇa ca|
mandare ruruvurghoraṃ siṃhaśārdūlakuñjarāḥ|| 133.11||
tūryārasitabdena tena te 'amitavikramāḥ|
abhindantaḥ svakaṃ vyūhaṃ yuyudhuḥ pramathāsurāḥ|| 133.12||
prathame saṃnipāte tu teṣāṃ yuddhe kṛtātmanām|
abhavaddāruṇo rāvo hastinām iva garjatām|| 133.13||
devāsurāḥ karasthaistu āyudhaiste sahasraśaḥ|
viśeṣayanti yuddhe sma parasparajighāṃsavaḥ|| 133.14||
tacchūlavajropalavṛkṣabāṇadṛḍhaprahārātiśayātiharṣam|
vivardhate pāriṣadāsurāṇāṃ yuddhaṃ yugaṃ tiṣyam ivātighoram|| 133.15||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe trayastriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 133.133||

skandapurana134
sanatkumāra uvāca|
saṃkule vartamāne tu pramathāsurasainyayoḥ|
śrūyante kārmukaravāḥ siṃhanādāśca dāruṇāḥ|| 134.1||
vyāviddhāṅgulayo devāścāraṇoragaguhyakāḥ|
neduruddhūtavastrāntā yuddhoddhavakṛtasvanāḥ|| 134.2||
śūrārasitaśabdena tenodīritavikramāḥ|
cakruḥ karmāṇyasahyāni darpitāḥ pramathāsurāḥ|| 134.3||
asibhirvyāyataiśchinnāḥ paṭṭiśirbhinnavakṣasaḥ|
śarasaṃkṛttamarmāṇaḥ patanti pramathāsurāḥ|| 134.4||
śirasāṃ patyamānānāṃ bāhūnāṃ corubhiḥ saha|
rāśayastatra dṛśyante pramathāsurasaṃyuge|| 134.5||
bhagnacakrā vidhvajāśca vivarūthā vikūbarāḥ|
dṛśyante śataśo vyaśvā hatasārathayo 'arathāḥ|| 134.6||
sapatākāḥ sakeyūrāḥ savarmāyudhaketavaḥ|
niṣkṛṣṭadantamuśalāḥ patanti gajapuṃgavāḥ|| 134.7||
śaraprahārarugṇāṅgāścāmarāpīḍakojjvalāḥ|
sasādino nipātyante hayāḥ sūryahayopamāḥ|| 134.8||
udbhrāntaisturagaistrastairdānavaiḥ sarathairapi|
tadbalaṃ prababhau mattaṃ bhrāntagrāhārṇavopamam|| 134.9||
vāsobhirātapatraiśca mukuṭairmaṇikuṇḍalaiḥ|
hārārdhahāraiḥ keyūrairaṅgulīyaiḥ sraguttamaiḥ|| 134.10||
karānanaiḥ prakṛttaiśca caraṇaiśca nipātitaiḥ|
yuddhabhūmirvṛtā bhāti dyaurnakṣatrairivoditaiḥ|| 134.11||
rudhirāsrāvavasanā nānābharaṇabhūṣaṇāḥ|
raktavastrāvṛtairgātrairmahī mṛtyurivābabhau|| 134.12||
atha vājigajaughānāṃ śoṇitodakavāhinī|
nadī pravavṛte ghorā yamasādanavāhinī|| 134.13||
mṛgahastikharāśvoṣṭramahāgrāhasamākulā|
māṃsamedoyakṛtpaṅkā dhanurdhvajaśatadrumā|| 134.14||
chinnaśīrṣopalaśatā hastapañcānanoragā|
keśaśaivālasaṃchannā dhanurjyāśatatantukā|| 134.15||
pāṇḍarāmbaraharṣā vai mukuṭātikulākulā|
bherīkacchapasaṃkīrṇā varābharaṇadardurā|| 134.16||
śaramīnasamākīrṇā khaḍganakradurāsadā|
rathacakramahānakrā gadayādoviloḍitā|| 134.17||
viśīrṇahārasikatā kaphasaṃjātapheninī|
raktotpalānāṃ māleva kauṅkumī sragivojjhitā|| 134.18||
jihvevoragarājasya yamasyājñā ivādbhutā|
bhayadā bhiruyodhānāṃ śūrāṇāṃ harṣavardhinī|
pravṛttā rudhirāmbhobhiḥ svargalokavahā nadī|| 134.19||
saṃrabdhadaityendravivṛddhadhūmaṃ nandīśvarāgnijvalitāntarālam|
babhau balaṃ sāgaratulyanādaṃ vināśi yadvajjagadantakāle|| 134.20||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe catustriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 134.134||

skandapurana135
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vivardhamāne saṃgrāme tasmin pāriṣadāsure|
girivyūhaprapātasthāḥ kruddhā dānavasattamāḥ|| 135.1||
te krodhācchūlaśaktyṛṣtigadāvarṣam atandritāḥ|
vavarṣuḥ pramathānīke varṣaṃ jaladharā iva|| 135.2||
śastravarṣeṇa patanāt tāḍyamānā hyanekaśaḥ|
acintayitvā tat sarvaṃ yuddhāyaiva mano dadhuḥ|| 135.3||
meghāḥ sasyāni hi yathā dviradāḥ pādapāniva|
pṛṣatāniva śārdūlāḥ śarabhā iva vāraṇān|| 135.4||
vajrā iva yathā śailān kāladūtā narāniva|
vighnāniva ca śāntyarthā nayānavinayā iva|| 135.5||
bhāvāniva yathā bhāvā doṣā doṣānyathāpi ca|
tathā nivātakavacān śūlaśaktyṛṣtivṛṣṭibhiḥ|
nijaghnuḥ pramathāḥ śūrāḥ śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|| 135.6||
śūlanirdāritoraskā muśalairbhinnamastakāḥ|
vajrāvaghātamlānāṅgā dānavāḥ patitā bhuvi|| 135.7||
teṣāṃ ninādāḥ śrūyante nadatām atidāruṇāḥ|
saṃvartakānāṃ meghānāṃ nadatām iva sarvataḥ|| 135.8||
iṣubhirbahudhā viddhā bhagnatrikakaśeravaḥ|
ceṣṭante hyasurā bhūmau bhagnapṛṣṭhā ivoragāḥ|| 135.9||
tato 'atikadanaṃ vīkṣya śūrastatra mahāsurāḥ|
nivṛttāḥ śataśastatra krodhasaṃraktalocanāḥ|| 135.10||
tairbhṛśaṃ pramathāste 'api viddhā vyāsa trapānvitāḥ|
saṃmīlitākṣā vṛṣabhā varṣaṃ nipatitaṃ yathā|| 135.11||
sahante tat tathā varṣaṃ pramathā dānaveritam|
te cāpi yuddhaṃ tumulaṃ kṛtvānte pīḍitāstadā|| 135.12||
bhagnāḥ parāṅmukhā jātāśchinnabhinnāṅgāsandhayaḥ|
tasmin bhagne 'atha sainye tu prāmathe pramathottamāḥ|| 135.13||
daśa cakrurmahāvegaṃ daśanāgaśatopamāḥ|
śaṅkukarṇaśca balavān ghaṇṭākarṇaśca vīryavān|| 135.14||
mahākālaśca kālābho nandiṣeṇaśca viśrutaḥ|
piṅgalo lohitākṣaśca somanandī ca vīryavān|| 135.15||
vināyakaśca -- -- -- nandī ca -- -- -- -- --|
chāgaḥ kuṇḍodaraḥ skando mayūravaram āsthitaḥ|| 135.16||
ete saha samunneduḥ payodā iva sāmbhasaḥ|
viviśuścāsuraṃ sainyaṃ samudraṃ makarā iva|| 135.17||
śaṅkukarṇahatā daityā ghaṇṭākarṇavidāritāḥ|
nandiṣeṇaśarābhyastā mahākālaprakālitāḥ|| 135.18||
kuṇḍodaragadāveśaiścūrṇitāstravibhūṣaṇāḥ|
piṅgalāloḍitā neśuḥ skandaśaktividāritāḥ|| 135.19||
muṣṭiprahārabhinnāsyaistalatāḍitamastakaiḥ|
apāhastaprahāraiśca kṣipyamāṇairitastataḥ|| 135.20||
viśastravastrakavacairmuktamūrdhajabandhanaiḥ|
prabhagnairdānavaistūrṇaṃ vyūhabhedo babhūva ha|| 135.21||
bhidyamāno girivyūho vibabhau ghoradarśanaḥ|
indravajrāhataḥ pūrvaṃ yathā vindhyo mahāgiriḥ|| 135.22||
bhinnavyūhāṃstato daityān pramathā jitakāśinaḥ|
dudruvuḥ śataśo vṛkṣān pakvāñchakunayo yathā|| 135.23||
tataḥ puno 'abhūdyuddhaṃ kolāhalasamākulam|
pramathānāṃ ca śūrāṇām asurāṇāṃ ca dāruṇam|| 135.24||
saṃnipāte punasteṣāṃ gajānām iva dāruṇe|
nedurdevāḥ sagandharvāḥ siddhāśca divi harṣitāḥ|| 135.25||
nānāvidhāstūryaravāstato dānavapārṣadaiḥ|
aśrūyanta kṛtā ghorā meghānāṃ nadatām iva|| 135.26||
gajaiśca nīlācalasaṃnikāśai rathaiśca gandharvavimānakalpaiḥ|
hayaiśca vāyupratimānavegaiścaranti daityāḥ samare hyabhītāḥ|| 135.27||
te śūlaśaktyṛṣtibhuśuṇḍibāṇaiḥ śailopalaiścakrasaśūlavajraiḥ|
anyonyam utsādayituṃ pravṛttā gaṇeśvarā dānavapuṃgavāśca|| 135.28||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe pañcatriṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 135.135||

ṣaṭtriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
virocanastu daityendro virocana ivoditaḥ|
viveśa pramathānīkaṃ meghānīkam ivāṃśumān|| 136.1||
mandarāgrapratīkāśam īṣādantaṃ kṣaranmadam|
caturdantaṃ samāsthāya dantinaṃ dantabhūṣitam|| 136.2||
sa nāgaskandhagastatra bhrājate 'asurapuṃgavaḥ|
udayāgraṃ samāsthāya sahasrāṃśurjvalanniva|| 136.3||
tomaraiḥ sa śaraiścāpi divākarakaraprabhaiḥ|
pramathānapatastāra śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|| 136.4||
vainateyo yathā nāgān siṃho govṛṣabhān yathā|
drāvayāmāsa pramathāṃstathā śūro virocanaḥ|| 136.5||
yāntam āyāntam aprāptaṃ prāptaṃ dūrastham eva ca|
pramathaṃ paśyate yaṃ yaṃ taṃ taṃ dārayate 'asuraḥ|| 136.6||
mṛgāḥ siṃhaṃ yathā dṛṣṭvā garuḍaṃ ca yathoragāḥ|
virocanaṃ tathā dṛṣṭvā pramathā dudruvurbhayāt|| 136.7||
gaṇeśvarabalaṃ dṛṣṭvā gaṇeśvaravaro drutam|
vināyakaḥ sannivṛttaḥ pramathānīkanāyakaḥ|| 136.8||
prasārayan karaṃ ghoraṃ pūrvam airāvato yathā|
virocanaṃ so 'abhyadhāvacchārdūlo hariṇaṃ yathā|| 136.9||
tam āpatantaṃ saṃvīkṣya tīkṣṇadantaṃ gajānanam|
kumbhāntare tomareṇa dārayāmāsa dānavaḥ|| 136.10||
taṃ tomaraṃ karāgreṇa niṣkṛṣya sa vināyakaḥ|
hastākṣiptena tenaiva virocanam adārayat|| 136.11||
sa tomareṇa nirbhinnaḥ karaghātāturaśca ha|
cacāla vihvalo raktaṃ cakṣāra ca virocanaḥ|| 136.12||
ghūrṇamānaṃ tadālakṣya dānavendraṃ virocanam|
dantābhyāṃ candraśubhrābhyāṃ nirbibheda vināyakaḥ|| 136.13||
vaināyakaṃ tat tu samīkṣya karma devāḥ saśakrā mumucuḥ praṇādān|
tasyottamāṅgopari puṣpamālā papāta devasya yathā trimārgā|| 136.14||
tayā tu nānāvidhapuṣpavatyā vibhāti devaḥ sa tadā srajā raṇe|
nakṣatramālāvalicāruśobhaḥ samunnato merurivāparaḥ sthitaḥ|| 136.15||
udbhinnaraktaṃ tu vidāryamāṇaṃ virocanaṃ vīkṣya vināyakena|
jambho 'ambudābho 'aturam ārasitvā dudrāva mā bhairiti bhāṣamāṇaḥ|| 136.16||
tam āpatantaṃ bahudhā nadantaṃ jambhaṃ viyanmegham ivāprameyam|
rurodha nandī samatāḍayacca vajreṇa vajrī kupito yathādrim|| 136.17||
sa vajraghātācchithilaḥ kriyāsu vyasuryathā dānavadevaputraḥ|
papāta bhūmau muhurutthitaśca ghṛtāvasiktaḥ sadasīva vahniḥ|| 136.18||
jambhe 'avasanne 'aribale prasanne ṣaḍdānavāḥ ṣaṇmukhapūrvajaṃ tam|
kuṭhāraśūlāsiparaśvadhaistu mlecchā yathā kruddhamukhāstatakṣuḥ|| 136.19||
vināyakastairavatakṣitastu prahlādidehāt pravikṛṣya dantau|
mumoca taṃ vai rudhirāvasiktaṃ rāhurvivasvantam ivārdhabhuktam|| 136.20||
sa tena mukto 'atirujāvṛtaśrīrvirocano nātibabhau manojñaḥ|
meghābhiruddho navameghakāle sampūrṇabimbo nabhasīva candraḥ|| 136.21||
vināyakābhān sa vināyakastu ṣaḍdānavān ṣaṇmukhasannikāśaḥ|
viśāladantāśanisamprahārairvyadrāvayat siṃha iva dvipendrān|| 136.22||
karīndravaktraḥ karam ucchrayitvā karī surāṇām iva jātadarpaḥ|
prākālayaddānavapuṃgavāṃstān yathā gajān darpitasiṃhapotaḥ|| 136.23||
siṃhekṣitānām iva gopatīnāṃ kālekṣitānām iva mānavānām|
vināyakenekṣitakālitānāṃ bhayaṃ tadāsīnmiṣatāṃ balānām|| 136.24||
yato yataḥ prekṣati vai sa devo hastīva hastaṃ svakam ucchrayitvā|
tatastato daityabalaṃ prabhagnaṃ caṇḍānileneva vanaṃ sapuṣpam|| 136.25||
dṛṣṭvā balaṃ tadbalinābhibhūtaṃ baleḥ suto 'asau balināṃ variṣṭhaḥ|
vināyakaṃ hantumanāḥ sasāra mattaṃ raṇe matta iva dvipendraḥ|| 136.26||
tam āpatantaṃ tapatām iveśaṃ kruddhaṃ raṇe kālam ivāttacāpam|
sasāra roddhuṃ samare ca yoddhuṃ kuṇḍodaraḥ siṃha ivānyasiṃham|| 136.27||
tau siṃhapotāviva jātadarpau prakīrṇahastāviva hastipotau|
samāgatau yuddharasābhimattau kuṇḍodaro vai balinandanaśca|| 136.28||
śatāni pañcaiva sa kārmukāṇāṃ vikṛṣya vajrāśaninisvanānām|
kuṇḍodarāyeṣuvarān sasarga garjan sa bāṇastu yathā payodaḥ|| 136.29||
tān āgatāṃstīkṣṇamukhāṃstadānīṃ bāṇasya bāṇān kupitāhikalpān|
kuṇḍodaraḥ śailaruheṇa sarvān manorathān vighna ivājaghāna|| 136.30||
tān niṣphalān prekṣya śarān surāriḥ suretarāriprahatān kṣitisthān|
śaktyā sa kuṇḍodaram ājaghāna śaktyā guhaḥ krauñcam ivācalendram|| 136.31||
vakṣaḥpradeśāt tu gaṇeśvarasya bāṇasya śaktiḥ kṣatajaṃ papau sā|
śakropanītaṃ ruciraṃ sugandhi yathāmṛtaṃ vajradharasya bhāryā|| 136.32||
śaktiprahārābhihatastu yakṣaḥ kuṇḍodaro dardaramandarābhaḥ|
papāta saṃjñāṃ vipulāṃ prahāya dāvāgninā dagdha ivoccavṛkṣaḥ|| 136.33||
kuṇḍodaraṃ taṃ nihataṃ samīkṣya vināyako 'asau cyutapadmamālaḥ|
dudrāva bāṇaṃ prati hantukāmaḥ karīva bhṛṅgārakarocchrayeṇa|| 136.34||
tam ānane vajranibhānanaiḥ śarairvināyakaṃ hi ātatam eva bāṇaḥ|
bibheda bhittvā ca tato rarāsa grīṣmavyapāye nabhasīva meghaḥ|| 136.35||
tṛṇāgrapātāniva seṣupātānacintayitvaiva gajendravaktraḥ|
īṣeṣa netraṃ savarūthacakraṃ babhañja bāṇasya rathaṃ sasūtam|| 136.36||
bāṇasya vāhāṃstu tam ārujantaṃ vināyakaṃ bhūmigataṃ yathebham|
siṃhīsutaḥ siṃha ivābhipatya sa bāhupāśena babandha rāhuḥ|| 136.37||
sa rāhuṇā bāhuyugāvabaddho vināyakaḥ sarpasahasramālaḥ|
praspandata bhrāmitapuṣkarāgro gajastaran devanadīṃ yathaiva|| 136.38||
taṃ rāhubāhupratibaddhaceṣṭaṃ vināyakaṃ vīkṣya tadā divisthāḥ|
devāḥ saśakrāḥ saha yakṣasiddhairhā heti hā hetyasakṛdvineduḥ|| 136.39||
kuṇḍodaro yakṣavarastu so 'atha āśvasya sasyaṃ hi yathāmbusiktam|
kuṭhāram ādāya jaghāna rāhuṃ jatrvantare saṃhatamuṣṭinā ca|| 136.40||
kuṭhāraghātāt sa tu muṣṭinā ca dṛḍhāhato yakṣavareṇa rāhuḥ|
vināyakaṃ bhīmabalo mumoca śubhetaraṃ karma yathā kulīnaḥ|| 136.41||
taṃ vai parāvṛtya karīva matto gajānanaḥ kānanaṣaṇḍavāsī|
padbhiśca dantaiśca jaghāna rāhuṃ prakīrṇahastena ca bhīmahastaḥ|| 136.42||
vināyakenābhihatastu rāhurdarpaṃ ca garvaṃ ca balaṃ ca hitvā|
nistoyameghapratimo 'amarāriḥ sthito yathā siṃhahato gajendraḥ|| 136.43||
rāhau tu kuṇḍodaramuṣṭighātairvināyakenaiva ca pīḍyamāne|
kujambhasaṃhrādamayāḥ satārā huṇḍastuhuṇḍaśca tadā tam īyuḥ|| 136.44||
mayastu kuṇḍodaram ājaghāna śūlena tāro meśalena kukṣau|
balastu lambāmbudasannikāśaṃ taṃ muṣṭinā vajranibhena cāpi|| 136.45||
hiraṇyanetrāvarajātmajaśca vināyakaṃ bhīmabalaṃ talena|
tasyātmajaścāpi jaghāna roṣāt sa cāpi gatvā balavāṃstuhuṇḍaḥ|| 136.46||
vināyakastaṃ tu tadā gṛhītvā kareṇa vikramya tuhuṇḍam ājau|
ākṣipya cotkṣipya ca bhīmavegaścikṣepa dūraṃ yamadūtakalpam|| 136.47||
prahrādam āhatya tataḥ sa devo mayaṃ ca mattāñjanatulyavakṣāḥ|
utpāṭya taṃ ghoraravaṃ nanāda śubhrāmbupūrṇo nabhasīva meghaḥ|| 136.48||
kuṇḍodaraścāpi balaṃ satāraṃ kujambham āhatya ca yakṣavaryaḥ|
ubhau raṇasthau gajayūthapālau vyādhūtamālau bhṛśajātakopau|| 136.49||
sasarjatustau śaravṛṣṭim ugrāṃ yathāmbuvṛṣṭiṃ jaladau sanādau|
tataḥ punaścāyudhasarjagāni payodavisphūrjitagarjitāni|
balāni tāni āsurapārṣadānāṃ saṃsaktabhāvaṃ paramaṃ gatāni|| 136.50||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
ṣaṭtriṃśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 136.136||

skandapurana137
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato vyatikaro bhūyaḥ pārṣadāsurasainyayoḥ|
sambabhūvodadhikṣobhānmakarāṇām ivādbhutaḥ|| 137.1||
paṭṭiśāsidhanuṣmanto vidyutvanta ivāmbudāḥ|
vibabhurdānavāstatra pramathāśca yuyutsavaḥ|| 137.2||
sahasva praharasveti naśya naṣṭastvam ityapi|
teṣām eva pravadatām aśrūyanta giro muhuḥ|| 137.3||
śūlaistriśūlaiścakraiśca huṇḍairlaguḍakampanaiḥ|
bhindipālaiḥ karasamaiḥ prasṛtairnikharairapi|| 137.4||
ṭaṅkaiḥ kaṭaṅkaiḥ prāsaiḥ pāśaiḥ paraśupaṭṭiśaiḥ|
drumopalaśilāghātairgirīṇāṃ śikharairapi|| 137.5||
etaiḥ praharaṇaiste vai sūdayanti parasparam|
ghaṇṭākarṇo 'aham asura jambho 'ahaṃ pramatheśvara|| 137.6||
somanandyaham indrāre kujambho 'ahaṃ gaṇādhipa|
bilvako 'aham ahaṃ yakṣa piṅgalo nāma dānava|| 137.7||
prahlādo 'aham ahaṃ nandī śaṅkukarṇo balo hyaham|
tvaṃ kaḥ kuṇḍodaro 'ahaṃ vai vṛtro 'ahaṃ kuṇḍakodara|| 137.8||
nandiṣeṇo 'asmyahaṃ śambhurmahākāla mayo hyaham|
viśākho 'ahaṃ baliraham ahaṃ bāṇo guho hyaham|| 137.9||
prahlādo 'aham ahaṃ śākho naigameṣo 'aham andhakaḥ|
ityevaṃ dānavānāṃ ca pramathānāṃ ca bhairavāḥ|| 137.10||
darpodrekādadhikṣepāḥ śrūyante yudhyatāṃ raṇe|
gajānām iva mattānāṃ meghānām iva cāgame|| 137.11||
bhidyatām iva śailānāṃ samudrāṇāṃ kṣayeṣviva|
pralayānteṣu mahatāṃ vāyūnāṃ javatām iva|| 137.12||
teṣām āsīnmahāñchabdaḥ parasparanijaghnuṣām|
brahmadaṇḍapratīkāśairyamadaṇḍanibhairapi|
āyudhaiḥ sūdayanti sma te 'anyonyakupitā bhṛśam|| 137.13||
vajrāṇām iva śaileṣu vaṃśānām iva dahyatām|
abhūccaṭacaṭāśabdaḥ śastrāṇāṃ pātyatāṃ tadā|| 137.14||
gaṇeśvaravimuktābhiḥ śaktibhiḥ sudṛḍhāhatāḥ|
nipeturārasantaste solkā iva yathā ghanāḥ|| 137.15||
drumaprahārabhagnāṅgā gadācūrṇitasandhayaḥ|
dānavā nipatantyurvyāṃ vājinaścyutajīvitāḥ|| 137.16||
chinnadhvajapatākeṣā bhagnākṣayugakabūrāḥ|
vidhvastāstatra dṛśyante vimānapratimā rathāḥ|| 137.17||
mātaṅgaiśca turaṅgaiśca syandanaiścāvacūrṇitaiḥ|
vindhyākrānteva sā bhūmirdurgamā samapadyata|| 137.18||
tatra devāḥ sagandharvāḥ sayakṣoragakiṃnarāḥ|
utkruṣṭavaraśabdāḍhyaṃ cakruḥ subahuśo 'ambaram|| 137.19||
divyānāṃ suvicitrāṇām amṛtopamagandhinām|
varṣaṃ papāta puṣpāṇāṃ yudhyante yatra te raṇe|| 137.20||
tathā tu te gajaghananādagarjanāḥ śarāsiśaktyṛṣṭigadāvisarjanāḥ|
parasparaṃ yuyudhuratīva saṃhatā diteḥ sutāḥ pramathagaṇāśca darpitāḥ|| 137.21||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe saptatriṃśottaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|| 137.137||

aṣṭatriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tāmyamāneṣu daityeṣu daityayūthapayūthapāḥ|
cakrurvegaṃ mahāvegā yugānteṣviva sāgarāḥ|| 138.1||
prahrādaścānuhrādaśca saṃhrādaḥ śinibāṣkalau|
prahlādasya ca ye putrāścatvāro bhīmavikramāḥ|| 138.2||
balirbāṇaśca vātaśca śambhuḥ kārtasvanaḥ kubhaḥ|
karabho namucistārastārakaścendratāpanaḥ|| 138.3||
añjano rūṣaṇo vyaṃso gaviṣṭhaḥ pṛthivīṃjayaḥ|
ilvakaḥ pilvakaścaiva dhundhurmūkaśca dānavaḥ|| 138.4||
kharo muro 'atha narakaḥ keśī dhenuka eva ca|
lambaḥ pralambo hyajaro bhāvayavyomamārdavāḥ|| 138.5||
vṛṣaparvā śatāvarto gavākṣo gomukhastathā|
saro nisundaḥ sundaśca mahābalaparākramāḥ|| 138.6||
pāko vipākaḥ santāpo hastī duryodhanastathā|
mohano mathanaścāpi sacakraścakra eva ca|| 138.7||
kālakāvadanaḥ kālaḥ kālanemī kalirdrumaḥ|
hayaśīrṣaścendraśirāstriśirāḥ śaṅkureva ca|| 138.8||
tathā gaganamūrdhā ca aviromā mahāmanaḥ|
asilomā tuhuṇḍaśca huṇḍo vṛtraśca dānavaḥ|| 138.9||
daśagrīvaśca bāliśca meghanīlaḥ prabhākaraḥ|
yaścādityarathāccakraṃ jahāra baladarpitaḥ|| 138.10||
sa vipracittiḥ sabalaḥ satyavartatadaṃśitaḥ (?)|
ete cānye ca ditijāḥ samadāste gajā iva|| 138.11||
cakrurutsāham utsartuṃ pramathya pramathān raṇe|
āmiṣārthe yathā siṃhā vāsitārthe yathā gajāḥ|| 138.12||
dānavā viviśustadvat pramathān saṃjighāṃsavaḥ|
teṣām āpatatāṃ vego bhīmo 'abhūddevavidviṣām|
sanakramakaro ghoro vegaḥ sindhupateriva|| 138.13||
te vai śastropalaśilāpādapāśanipāṇayaḥ|
pramathairuddhatai ruddhā nadīvegā ivārṇavaiḥ|| 138.14||
gaṇeśvarādhipo nandī mahākāyaśca vīryavān|
ghaṇṭākarṇaḥ śaṅkukarṇaḥ kuṇḍodaramahodarau|| 138.15||
nandiṣeṇaḥ somanandī karikaśca gaṇeśvaraḥ|
vighno vināyakaścaiva sa ca sarvavināyakaḥ|| 138.16||
piṅgalo lohitaścaiva mayūraḥ kukkuṭo 'api ca|
pañcākṣo vīrabhadraśca viṭpatiḥ pāvakārdanaḥ|| 138.17||
ādityāpyāyanaścaiva somāpyāyana eva ca|
samudrāpyāyanaścānyaḥ pāvakāpyāyanastathā|| 138.18||
varabarhidhvajaścaiva viśākhaḥ śākha eva ca|
naigameṣaśca balavān rudravīryaparākramāḥ|| 138.19||
bāhuleyodbhavā ye ca pramathā bhīmarūpiṇaḥ|
te 'abhyayurdānavān yuddhe vṛṣabhā vṛṣabhāniva|| 138.20||
teṣāṃ teṣāṃ ca saṃgrāmastumulaḥ samapadyata|
ajane gandhahastīnāṃ (?)śarabhairiva dāruṇaḥ|| 138.21||
mahāgajairiva gajāḥ parvatairiva parvatāḥ|
sāgarāḥ sāgarairyadvat pāvakairiva pāvakāḥ|| 138.22||
tathā surā jātadarpāḥ krodhavaiśvānarāvṛtāḥ|
dhṛtāḥ pāriṣadaiḥ śūrairvighnā dharmaparairiva|| 138.23||
ṭaṅkairvidāryamāṇāni giryagrāṇi samantataḥ|
gṛdhracakrāyamāṇāni patantyurvyāṃ sahasraśaḥ|| 138.24||
cakrāṇi cakraiśchidyante śūlaiḥ śūlā vidāritāḥ|
iṣubhiśceṣavo viddhāḥ patanti bhujagā iva|| 138.25||
vadanaiścandrapadmābhaiḥ karaiśca parighopamaiḥ|
āstṛtā medinī bhāti vyāghracarmāmbarairiva|| 138.26||
medomajjāsthipaṅkāṅkaṃ keśakaśmalasaṃkulam|
babhūvāyodhanaṃ ghoraṃ śmaśānavanasannibham|| 138.27||
hayā gajā rathāścāpi dānavānāṃ gaṇeśvaraiḥ|
saṃcūrṇitāḥ pradṛśyante tatra tatra mahītale|| 138.28||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
parīkṣaṇīyaḥ samitau tvam adya suretarāṇāṃ surarājaśatro|| 138.29||
nandinyathaivaṃ bruvatīndrakalpe śakrendruvāyupratitulyavīryaḥ|
baddhvā triśākhāṃ bhṛkuṭīṃ lalāṭe sa nandinaṃ prāha tadā kujambhaḥ|| 138.30||
vānarānana kiṃ vāgbhirmāṃ bhīṣayitum icchasi|
hiraṇyakaśipoḥ pautro nāhaṃ prākṛtadānavaḥ|| 138.31||
yam ātmadaṇḍādvaruṇāt sapāśādindrāt savajrāt sagadāddhaneśāt|
nāhaṃ raṇastho bhayam āharāmi bhayaṃ na daityeṣu palāyitaṃ vā|| 138.32||
adyeha te piṅgalalolanetraṃ mukhaṃ tvapātraṃ vikṛtāmanojñam|
madbāṇalūnaṃ patatām avanyāṃ tālādyathā tālaphalaṃ supakvam|| 138.33||
ityevam uktvā śarajālavṛṣṭyā nandīśvaraṃ dānavarājameghaḥ|
siṃho yathātīva vimucya nādaṃ prācchādayanmegha ivācalendram|| 138.34||
taruṃ yathā pakvaphalaṃ śakuntā valmīkam uccaṃ bhujagā ivogrāḥ|
tathā śarā dānavarājamuktā nandīśvaraṃ dīptamukhā viśanti|| 138.35||
vajreṇa vajrī sa tu tāñcharaughāñchailaḥ payodhāniva sannivārya|
kujambham uddiśya mumoca vajraṃ nanāda coccairnabhasīva meghaḥ|| 138.36||
tadvisphuliṅgodgataghorarūpaṃ samāhatārāvavimuktarāvam|
vajraṃ pradhāvatyasuraṃ nihantuṃ giriṃ yathā devatarājavajram|| 138.37||
tadvat sadantaiḥ suvipāṭavastaiḥ samīpagairdigdhavikarṇibhiśca|
jaghāna vajraṃ śatadhā kujambhaḥ saṃvartakāgniṃ samaye va meghaḥ|| 138.38||
tadbāṇavegaprahatātivegaṃ śailādinirmuktam amoghavegam|
vajraṃ kujambhābhihataṃ nivṛttaṃ dattaṃ yathonmādavikāradattam|| 138.39||
viṣṭambhitaṃ vajravaraṃ niśāmya niśāmya nādaṃ ca kujambhamuktam|
sasāra nandī kupito ripuṃ taṃ rāhuryathā vai khatale tamondhram|| 138.40||
balāt sa saṃgṛhya rathaṃ kareṇa īṣāvarāgre pramatheśapālaḥ|
ākṣipya cikṣepa sasūtavāhaṃ kṣiptvā ca bhūyaḥ sa rarāsa ghoram|| 138.41||
sambhrāntacakraḥ savisandhitāśvaḥ prabhraṣṭasūtāsiśirogranemiḥ|
kujambhavāhaḥ khatalāt papāta giriryathā vajranikṛttapakṣaḥ|| 138.42||
tasmādrathānnandigajapranunnādapetya prahrādiradīnasattvaḥ|
śaktiṃ samādāya na dīnasattvastasthau savidyut saravo yathābdaḥ|| 138.43||
tāṃ sarpajihvām iva lelihānāṃ mṛtyuṃ kṣudhārtām iva bhoktukāmām|
śikhāṃ mahāgneriva dīpyamānāṃ sa nandine sampramumoca jambhaḥ|| 138.44||
sā śaktirindrāribhujapramuktā ugrātidīptāṅgirasīva kṛtyā|
abhyāhatā nandimukhānalena dagdhā pataṅgīva yathānalena|| 138.45||
śaktiṃ sa dagdhvā vadanānalena kapīndravaktrastapanaprabhāvaḥ|
vajreṇa taṃ satvaram ājaghāna vajreṇa meruṃ bhagavānivendraḥ|| 138.46||
sa vajraghātādavacūrṇitāsthiḥ saṃśīrṇadantekṣaṇabhagnajānuḥ|
kubjaḥ kujambho nipapāta bhūmau śakreṇa vajrābhihato yathādriḥ|| 138.47||
tasmin hate devagaṇā vineduḥ sarve surāṇām arayaśca daityān|
bhūtādhipaṃ bhūtapatiśca devaṃ prapūjayāmāsa śaśāṅkacihnam|| 138.48||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe jambhavadhe
aṣṭatriṃśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 138.138||

ūnacatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
kujambhaṃ nihataṃ dṛṣṭvā nandinā devanandinā|
ninādaṃ cakrire devāścāraṇāśca mahoragāḥ|| 139.1||
tena devaninādena kujambhanidhanena ca|
jambho dānavaśārdūlaḥ krodham āhārayanmahat|| 139.2||
tasya kruddhasya gātrebhyo niṣpetuḥ pāvakārciṣaḥ|
merorvajrāhatasyeva visphuliṅgāḥ samantataḥ|| 139.3||
solkāmbudanibhābhāso jambhaḥ krodhasamāvṛtaḥ|
dudrāva nandinaṃ hantuṃ kuñjaraṃ siṃharāḍiva|| 139.4||
so 'ardhabhārasahasrasya kṛtaṃ saikyāyasaṃ mahat|
udvahan parighaṃ ghoraṃ daityo dudrāva nandinam|| 139.5||
tiṣṭhedānīṃ durācāra mayā dṛṣṭaḥ kva yāsyasi|
eṣa tvāṃ vajrasaṃkāśaḥ parighaścūrṇayiṣyati|| 139.6||
ityuktvā ghorayā vācā jambho nandinam agrataḥ|
parighaṃ tasya cikṣepa daṇḍaṃ yama ivāparaḥ|| 139.7||
sa tasya karanirmukto nirmuktoragasannibhaḥ|
parigho nandinaṃ yāti hantuṃ kālānalopamaḥ|| 139.8||
taṃ vāsukibhujaṅgābhaṃ brahmadaṇḍanibhaṃ mahat|
vajreṇābhyahanannandī devarājo yathā balam|| 139.9||
vajraprahāraṃ tṛṇavadvicintya parighaḥ sa tu|
śakrāgniriva durdṛśyaḥ pradhāvan nandinaṃ prati|| 139.10||
kṛto ninādaḥ sumahat pramathaiśca sahasraśaḥ|
śrutvā ninādaṃ devānāṃ parighaṃ vīkṣya cāgatam|| 139.11||
śaṅkukarṇo 'abhidudrāva parighaṃ prati vegitaḥ|
sa taṃ karkoṭakaprakhyaṃ durnivāryaṃ mahāstravat|| 139.12||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
śaṅkukarṇena parighaṃ gṛhītaṃ vīkṣya tadbalāt|| 139.13||
vinedurmuditā devāḥ śaṅkukarṇaṃ ca tuṣṭuvuḥ|
śaṅkukarṇo 'api parighaṃ gṛhītvā balavān punaḥ|| 139.14||
rarāsa jambham uddi'sya sasāra ca raṇapriyaḥ|
tato dānavaśārdūlaḥ sasāra raṇalālasaḥ|| 139.15||
tato gaṇeśvarabale dānavānāṃ bale tathā|
jajñe vāditraninadaḥ siṃhanādavimiśritaḥ|| 139.16||
atha gaganatale babhūva śabdaḥ kṣubhitasamudrapayodanādakalpaḥ|
danutanayagaṇādhipeśayuddhaṃ tadupaniśamya divaukasāṃ tadānīm|| 139.17||
pramathagaṇavarāḥ sanāgarudrā hyasuravarāśca sahāndhakā raṇasthāḥ|
vyuparatakalahāstadāvatasthurgaṇapatidānavayuddham īkṣamāṇāḥ|| 139.18||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
ūnacatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 139.139||

catvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śaṅkukarṇaṃ tu dhāvantaṃ jambhaṃ prati mahābalaḥ|
vṛtro 'abhyadhāvat taṃ hantuṃ pañcānana iva dvipam|| 140.1||
utsṛjya śaṅkukarṇo 'api jambhaṃ gaṇapapuṅgavaḥ|
vṛtram evābhidudrāva vighāto vai damaṃ yathā|| 140.2||
parigheṇāhanaccainaṃ śaṅkukarṇo gaṇeśvaraḥ|
mahāgiriṃ yathā śakro vajreṇa śataparvaṇā|| 140.3||
vṛtro 'api cātha daityendraḥ parigheṇāyasena vai|
babhrāma tāḍito 'atyarthaṃ vāyununna iva drumaḥ|| 140.4||
sa tena suprahāreṇa rudhirasrāvacitritaḥ|
svarṇadhāturasodgārī nīlācala ivābabhau|| 140.5||
vṛtre ghūrṇati daityendre parighābhihate bhṛśam|
vinedurdevagandharvāḥ pūjayanto gaṇeśvaram|| 140.6||
tataścirāt samāśvasya vṛtro dānavapuṃgavaḥ|
gireḥ śṛṅgaṃ samutpāṭya śaṅkukarṇam adhāvata|| 140.7||
sa tasya tat savṛkṣarkṣaṃ sadhātūpalapannagam|
gaṇeśvarāyācalāgraṃ cikṣepa ca rarāsa ca|| 140.8||
tadvṛtrabhujanirmuktaṃ giryagraśikharaṃ mahat|
bibheda nandī vajreṇa keśarīva mataṅgajam|| 140.9||
atha tau gaṇadaityendrau bhujairbhujagakopanau|
sametau ghorasaṃhrādau niyuddhakuśalāvubhau|| 140.10||
niṣṭanantāvivādityau dīpyamānāvivānalau|
garjamānāviva ghanau bṛṃhantāviva kuñjarau|| 140.11||
mattāviva ca śārdūlau niḥśvasantāvivoragau|
nardamānau yathā siṃhau valgamānau vṛṣāviva|| 140.12||
calantāviva śailendrau ghūrṇamānāvivārṇavau|
pūrayantau yathā meghau spardhantau makarāviva|| 140.13||
ityevaṃ śaṅkukarṇaśca vṛtraścāsurapuṃgavaḥ|
prayuddhau yuddhakuśalau parasparajighāṃsayā|| 140.14||
muṣṭibhirvajrakalpaiśca talaiścāśanisannibhaiḥ|
pādaprahārairghoraiśca ūrdhvam utkṣepaṇaistathā|| 140.15||
ākṣepairatha vikṣepaiḥ karṣaṇairapakarṣaṇaiḥ|
pauruṣākhyāpanairugrairnāmasaṃśravaṇairapi|| 140.16||
karajāgrapratudanairgalagrahaṇanigrahaiḥ|
siṃhanādaiḥ savāditrairvṛkṣaśailaśilopalaiḥ|| 140.17||
śaṅkukarṇo gaṇādhyakṣaḥ sa ca vṛtro danoḥ sutaḥ|
jaghnatustāvathānyonyam anyonyasyāntaraiṣiṇau|| 140.18||
śaṅkukarṇena vṛtrastu dṛḍhamūla iva drumaḥ|
hastāvabandhanotkṣiptaḥ sahasā pātitaḥ kṣitau|| 140.19||
tato gaṇeśvarabale dānavānāṃ tathā bale|
sādhuśabdo babhūvoccairvṛtre tu vinipātite|| 140.20||
muṣṭinā tam athāhatya vṛtraṃ bhuvi nipātya ca|
śaṅkukarṇo hyapakrānto dejājjīva ivāśugaḥ|| 140.21||
vṛtrastu sumahāvīryo muṣṭitāḍanavihvalaḥ|
indraketurivottasthau dudrāva ca gaṇeśvaram|| 140.22||
tam āpatantaṃ vṛkṣeṇa śaṅkukarṇo gaṇeśvaraḥ|
śālena tāḍayāmāsa ita ehīti cābravīt|| 140.23||
kruddhena śaṅkukarṇena vṛtro vai śālatāḍitaḥ|
upetya pāde jagrāha śaṅkukarṇaṃ balī balāt|| 140.24||
śaṅkukarṇsaṃ gṛhītvā tu vṛtro nāga ivāṇḍajam|
bhrāmayāmāsa vivaśaṃ lokaṃ moha ivodyataḥ|| 140.25||
śaṅkukarṇasya vṛtreṇa bhrāmyamāṇasya sarvaśaḥ|
śarīrāt samadīryanta bhūṣaṇāni sahasraśaḥ|| 140.26||
taṃ bhrāmyamāṇaṃ prasamīkṣya devā vṛtreṇa sarve ca tadā gaṇeśaḥ|
hā heti kṛtvā dhṛtaśastrabāṇāḥ pradudruvustasya vimokṣaṇārtham|| 140.27||
āgacchatastān prasamīkṣya vṛtraḥ sarvān gaṇeśāñchitiśastrahastān|
mumoca taṃ saṃsadi śaṅkukarṇaṃ nāgaṃ garutmāniva pakṣirājaḥ|| 140.28||
vṛtramuktastu gaṇapaḥ śaṅkukarṇo mahābalaḥ|
yoddhukāmaḥ punarvṛtraṃ nivṛtto hastirāḍiva|| 140.29||
tataḥ punaḥ siṃharavāḥ samantāt tasmin bale dundubhinisvanāśca|
he śaṅkukarṇeti ca sādhuvādo manoharastasya raṇe babhūva|| 140.30||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
catvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 140.140||

ekacatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śaṅkukarṇaṃ bhrāmayitvā vṛtrastyaktvā ca bhūtale|
mamarda pramathānīkaṃ vanaṃ matto yathā gajaḥ|| 141.1||
sa nandinaṃ nandiṣeṇaṃ somanandinam eva ca|
āhatya drāvayitvā ca nanarda jalado yathā|| 141.2||
tasyātha nardamānasya viṭpatii rudrasattamaḥ|
mumoca vajrāgnisamaṃ ripukṣayakaraṃ śaram|| 141.3||
sa viṭpativinirmuktaḥ śaro ravikaraprabhaḥ|
viveśa vṛtraṃ nirdārya siddho 'amudam ivāmbare|| 141.4||
ucchritya svakaraṃ so 'atha karaṃ hastīva dānavaḥ|
viṭpatiṃ dudruve saṃkhye payodam iva mārutaḥ|| 141.5||
taṃ śūlena mahākāyo nandī vajreṇa dānavam|
somanandī kuṭhāreṇa nandiṣeṇastalena ca|| 141.6||
bāṇānāṃ ca sahasreṇa viṭpatirvṛtram āhave|
bibheda paramakruddhaḥ punaścānyaistrisaptabhiḥ|| 141.7||
so 'ardito gaṇayūtheśairdānavaḥ parvatopamaḥ|
pātyamāno rarāsoccaiḥ sadaivata iva drumaḥ|| 141.8||
atha mayabalamūkatārajambhā namucigaṇelvalabāṇabāṇaputrāḥ|
vividhaśaravarāyudhāvatasthurgaṇapativīratamaṃ nivārayantaḥ|| 141.9||
rucirakanakacāruhāraśobhāścalavalāyābharaṇā mahendrakalpāḥ|
ditivaratanayātihṛṣṭarūpāḥ pramathabaleṣu caranti kālarūpāḥ|| 141.10||
muśalahalaśarāvadāritāsyā giriśikharāśanivajracūrṇitāṅgāḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 141.11||
vraṇajapṛṣatavipruṣokṣitāścyutasitahāravibhūṣaṇasrajaḥ|
bhayacakitamukhāḥ pradudruvuste pramathagaṇā ripubhirbhṛśārditāḥ|| 141.12||
divi sitavirajā yathocchritā navalajadā navatoyavṛṣṭayaḥ|
visasṛjururuvegadāruṇā dititanayāḥ śaravṛṣṭim ardanīm|| 141.13||
atha karigirimeghasannibhā jvalanadivākaratulyatejasaḥ|
vimalaśitavisṛṣṭabāṇajālāḥ pramathagaṇān praharanti daityamukhyāḥ|| 141.14||
atha parighaśarāsipaṭṭiśaiḥ karavarayantraśatapraniḥsṛtaiḥ|
tridaśaripubhayapradā raṇe samaram upetya vicakramurgaṇāḥ|| 141.15||
giriśikharanibhāśca dantivaryā drutagamanā bahavaśca vājimukhyāḥ|
surasadananibhā rathāśca bhīmāḥ samaramukhe nipatanti bhagnadagdhāḥ|| 141.16||
iṣuvadanadṛḍhāvatakṣitā vraṇajasamukṣitasūkṣmavāsasaḥ|
prasṛtanayanasattvajīvitā danutanayāḥ śataśo 'avapothitāḥ|| 141.17||
cyutasitavarahārakuṇḍalairmukuṭakirīṭamaṇisragambaraiḥ|
samaramukhamahī virājate ruciravarābharaṇairivorvaśī|| 141.18||
kṣubhita iva yathā mahārṇavo jalasamaye ca yathā nabho mahat|
asuragaṇabalaṃ tathābhavat prajavitavāraṇavājidānavam|| 141.19||
yamavaruṇadhaneśavāsavā bhagavasusūryaśaśāṅkamārutāḥ|
hṛṣitanayanavaktrapaṅkajā rurudhuramitragaṇārdanoddhatāḥ|| 141.20||
pravicaritagajendratoyadaṃ turagavidhāvitavāyusaṃcaram|
aśaniśaraśatahradāvilaṃ na tu virarāma raṇāntadurdinam|| 141.21||
kamaladalanikāśalocanaiḥ kamaladivākaracandrasannibhaiḥ|
danutanayavarānanairmahī prativibabhau kamalairivāvṛtā|| 141.22||
vimathitagaṇadānaveśvaraṃ rudhiravapāmadasekarūṣitam|
samaram atisuraudradāruṇaṃ garuḍapiśācabalāvalokitam|| 141.23||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
ekacatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 141.141||

dvicatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tasmin vartati saṃgrāme pramathāsurasainyayoḥ|
dhanuṣāṃ śrūyate śabdaḥ prāvṛḍambudharopamaḥ|| 142.1||
garjatāṃ ca gajendrāṇāṃ hreṣatāṃ caiva vājinām|
yuddhagāndharvaraktānāṃ nādāścāmararakṣasām|| 142.2||
śrotrāyāsakarā ghorā vajrāśaniravā iva|
śrūyante hi vivardhante hyarthā hi ādharmaṇām iva (?)|| 142.3||
tataḥ kārtasvano nāma dānavo meghanisvanaḥ|
jaghāna pramathān yuddhe kālo martyānivāgataḥ|| 142.4||
sa rathī kārmukī bāṇī kavacī kuṇḍalī tathā|
pramathānīkam adahacchuṣkaṃ tṛṇam ivānalaḥ|| 142.5||
kārtasvanadhanurmuktāḥ kārtasvanamahāśarāḥ|
pramathān dārya niḥsaṅgān dārayanti raṇāvanim|| 142.6||
śalabhā iva kedārānanayā iva mānavān|
khagā iva tarūn pakvān garuḍaḥ pannagāniva|| 142.7||
tathā te pṛthavo bāṇāḥ kārtasvanadhanuścyutāḥ|
pramathān vyākulīcakrurvāsavṛkṣānivāṇḍajāḥ|| 142.8||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
śaravrātā gaṇānīke nipatanti girāviva|| 142.9||
praśāntavādyaninadaṃ śaraghātātivejitam|
gaṇeśvarabalaṃ jajñe bandhujīvavanaṃ yathā|| 142.10||
ghanāniva yathā vāyurvainateya ivoragān|
pṛṣatāniva śārdūlastamaughāniva bhāskaraḥ|| 142.11||
tathā kārtasvanaḥ kruddhaḥ śaravajraiḥ sudāruṇaiḥ|
nirdadāha gaṇādhyakṣā/llokān saṃvartako yathā|| 142.12||
gaṇeśvarabalaṃ dṛṣṭvā dagdhaṃ jagdhaṃ rujāturam|
viṭpatiḥ kupito devaḥ kārtasvanam athābravīt|| 142.13||
śarapāte 'atha saṃsthityā rudro rudraparākramaḥ|
dānavendraṃ prakupito niṣaṅgāduddharañcharam|| 142.14||
kārtasvana balaṃ vīryaṃ pratāpaśca tavottamaḥ|
kim etānabalāṃ haṃsi dānavendra gaṇeśvarān|| 142.15||
āgaccha yadi te śaktiryadi vā vidyate balam|
mayā kuruṣva saṃmardaṃ mā nardaḥ paśya me balam|| 142.16||
kuṇḍalālaṃkṛtaṃ te 'adya daṃṣṭrāṅkuravibhūṣaṇam|
pātayāmi śiro daitya tālādvātaḥ phalaṃ yathā|| 142.17||
yadyapi tvādya rakṣanti dānavāḥ sāndhakā raṇe|
tathāpi te hariṣyāmi prāṇānasurapāṃsana|| 142.18||
ityevaṃ nardamānasya viṭpaterdānavo nadan|
sasarja bāṇaṃ muktvā ca jagarja jalado yathā|| 142.19||
jvalamānaḥ sa tu śaro ghṛtasikta ivānalaḥ|
gharmārkasadṛśo bhāsā prādhāvadviṭpatiṃ prati|| 142.20||
niṣprabho 'arko 'abhavat tatra tasya bhāsā patatriṇaḥ|
kārtasvananinādena patanti vihagāḥ kṣitau|| 142.21||
so 'api bhāsā yuto bāṇaḥ saṃvartaka ivānalaḥ|
viṭpateḥ kaṅkaṇe magno niraye duṣkṛtī yathā|| 142.22||
tatastam eva niṣkṛṣya dānavaprahitaṃ śaram|
kārtasvanāya cikṣepa viṭpatirvinanāda ca|| 142.23||
sa viṭpativinirmuktaḥ śaro dānavanāśakṛt|
dānavasya śiro yanturjahāreṣupathān daśa|| 142.24||
hate yantari tasyāśvāścapalāḥ śabalā raṇe|
udbhrāntā ratham ādāya śyenā iva yathāmiṣam|| 142.25||
kārtasvanarathaṃ yāta kim āsata nigṛhṇata|
ityevaṃ dānavendrāṇāṃ babhūva ninado mahān|| 142.26||
vistīrṇe mandaraprasthe bhraman bhāti rathottamaḥ|
sāditya iva saptāśvo merau rathavaro bhraman|| 142.27||
avaplutya tatastasmāddrutāśvādrathasattamāt|
kārtasvano dhanuṣpāṇirabhidudrāva viṭpatim|| 142.28||
balayostu tato nādaḥ sādhu dāhviti sambabhau|
kārtasvane yoddhukāme bhūyo viṭpatinā saha|| 142.29||
sa viṭpatiṃ vajranibhairbahubhirniśitaiḥ śaraiḥ|
dānavo 'avākiranmegho yathā dhārotkarairgirim|| 142.30||
sa kārtasvanabāṇaughairghanaughairiva sāgaraḥ|
viṭpatiḥ pūryamāṇo 'api vyathāṃ naiva tadāgamat|| 142.31||
ā karṇāt kārmukaṃ so 'atha vikṛṣya balavān balāt|
ciccheda daityendraśarān dvidhaikaikaṃ tridhā tathā|| 142.32||
tāniṣūñchātayitvā tu patribhiḥ prāṇabhojanaiḥ|
kārtasvanaṃ sahasreṇa bibheda ca nanāda ca|| 142.33||
pṛṣṭhato dṛśyamānāsyaiḥ śaraistairdānavo babhau|
yathācalo nāgavarairvivarārdhavinirgataiḥ|| 142.34||
athāsya kārmukaṃ khaḍgaṃ śarāvāpaṃ ca pañcakam|
ciccheda rudraḥ saṃkruddhastaṃ ca so 'abhyardayadbalī|| 142.35||
atha bāṇam indrakuliśena samaṃ kupitaṃ śvasantam iva nāgapatim|
visasarja viṭpatirudārabalo ditinandanārdanam ajihmagatim|| 142.36||
śararāṭ sa rudravarasamprahitaḥ samarāṅgaṇe visṛtadhūmalavaḥ|
asurānanaṃ yudhi jahāra balāt kamalaṃ yathā munirudāramatiḥ|| 142.37||
atha daivatairmunivaraiśca kṛtaḥ pramathaiśca bhīmaninadairninadaḥ|
tadarermukhaṃ hṛtam udīkṣya tadā vaḍavāmukhāgnidamanena raṇe|| 142.38||
sa tu viṭpatiḥ pramathasainyapatistvabhisṛtya bhūtapatinā suciram|
abhipūjitaḥ samarakarmapaṭustridaśārisiṃhadamano damanaḥ|| 142.39|
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
dvicatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 142.141||

tricatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
kārtasvanam ariṃ hatvā kārtasvaramaheṣuṇā|
dadāha viṭpatirdaityānanalaḥ śalabhāniva|| 143.1||
sa vyāyatadhanurdevaścārukāñcanakuṇḍalaḥ|
jagarjeṣūn dānaveṣu sṛjan sūryaḥ karāniva|| 143.2||
te kāñcanamayaiḥ puṅkhairgaruḍāṅgaruhacchadaiḥ|
daivasṛṣṭā ivānarthā dānaveṣvapatañcharāḥ|| 143.3||
chinnānanāśchinnakarāśchinnapādodaroravaḥ|
dānavāḥ śataśaḥ petuḥ kṣitau kṣitidharā yathā|| 143.4||
pṛṣṭheṣvabhihatāḥ kecit kecit pārśveṣu dāritāḥ|
nayaneṣvapare viddhā bhramantyandhā ivāpare|| 143.5||
mṛgāniva ca śārdūlo garuḍaḥ panagāniva|
kṛtaghnaḥ sukṛtānīva tamāṃsīva divākaraḥ|| 143.6||
tathā tānasurān devo viṭpatiḥ pāvakārdanaḥ|
anāśayata tīkṣṇāgraiḥ śarairvajrānalānanaiḥ|| 143.7||
virathāḥ pātitagajāḥ śarāturaturaṅgamāḥ|
dhāvante dānavāstrastā viṭpateḥ śaravejitāḥ|| 143.8||
atha dṛṣṭvāsurabalaṃ muktaśastrayaśombaram|
bhagnaṃ viṭpatinā yuddhe gajeneva yathā vanam|| 143.9||
ye ye balotkaṭāstatra prakhyātāśca suretarāḥ|
abhidrutā viṭpatinā siṃhenevaitare mṛgāḥ|| 143.10||
prahrādaścānuhrādaśca saṃhrādaḥ śinibāṣkalau|
jambho virocano bāṇo baliścaiva sa dānavaḥ|| 143.11||
ajako namucirvysaṃsaḥ ilvako vilvakastathā|
vipracittistuhuṇḍuśca huṇḍo vakraśca dānavaḥ|| 143.12||
mayastārastārakākṣo vidyunmālī prabhañjanaḥ|
ariṣṭaścaiva riṣṭaśca añjano rūśabhaḥ kubhaḥ|| 143.13||
kālaśca kālanemiśca kālakāvadanastathā|
sampātirilvalaścāpi balo naraka eva ca|| 143.14||
madhukaiṭabhayoḥ putrau dhundhurmūkaśca dānavaḥ|
hastirvipākaḥ pākaśca vikarṇaḥ śambhureva ca|| 143.15||
udyatairbahubhiḥ śastrairulkāpātasamaprabhaiḥ|
viṭpatiṃ dudruvuḥ kruddhāḥ siṃhā iva vineduṣaḥ|| 143.16||
te taṃ śūlopalairhuṇḍaiḥ sāyakaiścāśanisvanaiḥ|
nijaghnurbhīmaninadāḥ payodā iva parvatam|| 143.17||
toyavṛṣṭiṃ yathā meghā visṛjantyanaleritāḥ|
sasṛjurdānavā deve śaravṛṣṭiṃ tathaiva te|| 143.18||
tāṃ śastravṛṣṭim āmitrīm amitragaṇamardanaḥ|
acchinadviṭpatistūrṇaṃ samprītiṃ kalaho yathā|| 143.19||
tataste danudaiteyā viyatsthā viṭpatiṃ prati|
nardamānā ivāmbhodā girivarṣaṃ sṛjantyuta|| 143.20||
anye ca mandarāgrasthā mandārasragivāsthitāḥ|
mumucuḥ sālasaralān devadārūṃśca viṭpatau|| 143.21||
so 'ambarasthaiḥ kṣitisthaiśca dānavairdṛḍham arditaḥ|
viṭpatirvimukho jajñe toyasikta ivānalaḥ|| 143.22||
viṭpatiṃ vimukhaṃ dṛṣṭvā dānavaiḥ parvataiścitam|
na marṣeyurbhīmabalāḥ prakhyātā ye gaṇeśvarāḥ|| 143.23||
somanandī ca nandī ca nandiṣeṇaśca pārṣadaḥ|
prabhāmayo vīrabhadraḥ sūryāpyāyana eva ca|| 143.24||
pañcākṣaḥ kopapālaśca trinetraḥ piṅgalekṣaṇaḥ|
rākṣasaḥ piṅgalaścaiva śmaśānanilayo 'annadaḥ|| 143.25||
ghaṇṭākarṇaḥ śaṅkukarṇaḥ sa ca kuṇḍodaro balī|
airāvatamukhaścaiva annapālaḥ kapāladhṛk|| 143.26||
ete cānye ca gaṇapāḥ śataśaḥ śabditā gaṇaiḥ|
viviśurdānavān dagdhuṃ drumāñchuṣkānivānalāḥ|| 143.27||
te viṭpatiṃ samparivārya sarve gajendrapotā iva garjamānāḥ|
triśūlacakreṣubhuśuṇḍihastā gaṇeśvarā yuddhadhiyaḥ pratīyuḥ|| 143.28||
teṣāṃ ca teṣāṃ ca tato babhūva saṃsaktayuddhaṃ samaroddhatānām|
madoddhatānāṃ sahavāsitānāṃ mahāgajānām iva kānaneṣu|| 143.29||
taṃ dānavānāṃ sagaṇeśvarāṇāṃ mukhyāhavaṃ vīkṣya divaukasāste|
cerurnabho divyavimānayānaiḥ sahiṃsanādāḥ satalābhighātāḥ|| 143.30||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
tricatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 143.141||

catuścatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
te 'atisaṃrambhasaṃyuktā darpitāḥ pramathāsurāḥ|
saṃsaktayuddhaṃ yuyudhuḥ parasparakṛtāgasaḥ|| 144.1||
śaktyullālitahastena kumāreṇāvaniṃjayaḥ|
kālanemiḥ kālakalpo viśākhaṃ samayodhayat|| 144.2||
yaścādityarathāccakraṃ jahāra baladarpitaḥ|
sa vipracittiḥ śākhena saṃsakto yuddhalālasaḥ|| 144.3||
naigameṣo hayagrīvaṃ sugrīvaṃ dānavādhipam|
yodhayāmāsa so 'agneyo madhuṃ madhunihā yathā|| 144.4||
prāyudhyan nandinā jambhastuhuṇḍaḥ somanandinā|
huṇḍo vināyakaṃ śūram ayodhayata dāvanaḥ|| 144.5||
mahākāyastu kālena ghanena namuciḥ saha|
piṅgalābhyāṃ gaṇeśābhyām ilvakaḥ pilvakaḥ sa ca|| 144.6||
śaṅkukarṇena hrādastu hyanuhrādena viṭpatiḥ|
ādityāpyāyano rudraḥ saṃhrādena samāgataḥ|| 144.7||
kuṇḍodaraśca yakṣendro ghaṇṭākarṇaśca pārṣadaḥ|
balelvakābhyāṃ saṃsaktau siṃhābhyām iva kuñjarau|| 144.8||
pañcākṣeṇa baliḥ sārdhaṃ rudreṇādityavarcasā|
balerjanayitā sakto vīrabhadreṇa dānavaḥ|| 144.9||
sumukhena mayaḥ sārdhaṃ tāro durmukham āsarat|
mayūro vajraromāṇaṃ kukkuṭo muram āgamat|| 144.10||
śeṣā hyapi gaṇādhyakṣāḥ śeṣairdaityaiḥ samāgatāḥ|
paraspareṇa saṃsaktā gajāḥ siṃhairivāhave|| 144.11||
dahyatām iva veṇūnāṃ vijane kṛṣṇavartmanā|
abhūt taṭataṭāśabdaḥ śastrāṇāṃ vinipātyatām|| 144.12||
mā dravīrdrava tiṣṭheti paśya paśyeti vādinaḥ|
anyonyam abhijaghnuste saṃsaktā gaṇadānavāḥ|| 144.13||
vapāmedobhidigdhāṅgāśchinnānanakaroravaḥ|
dānavāḥ pramathāścaiva hyadhāvañchastramakṣitāḥ|| 144.14||
ānanairurubhiḥ pādaiḥ karadantekṣaṇairapi|
hārairvikīrṇaiḥ keyūraiḥ sragambaravibhūṣaṇaiḥ|| 144.15||
gajendrāstaparistomaiḥ kambalairāyudhairapi|
rarāja sa raṇoddeśo nabhastārāgrahairiva|| 144.16||
nakhadantāgrajanitaiścitraiḥ kṣatajabindubhiḥ|
raktacandanadigdhāṅgī bhūmiḥ strīriva nirbabhau|| 144.17||
vināyakasya sa śaraṃ tuhuṇḍuḥ sūryatejasam|
preṣayitvā jahāsoccaiḥ kopaṃ tasya vivardhayan|| 144.18||
tasyāpi hasato vaktraṃ bṛhatkuṇḍalamaṇḍitam|
asinā tīkṣṇadhāreṇa ciccheda sa vināyakaḥ|| 144.19||
tuhuṇḍaṃ nihataṃ dṛṣṭvā huṇḍo bhrātṛvadhāturaḥ|
śaktiṃ cikṣepa nāgāsye śakro 'aśanim ivācale|| 144.20||
vināyakasya sā śaktirmaṇau maṇiśatācitā|
patitāsṛk papau krodhājjvaladagniśikhopamā|| 144.21||
vināyakasya sā kroḍe lagnā śaktirvinirbabhau|
indranīlaṃ maṇiṃ prāpya rekhā cāmīkarī yathā|| 144.22||
sa huṇḍaśaktiṃ karapuṣkareṇa nikṛṣya devo raviraśmikalpām|
tayaiva huṇḍaṃ sahasā jaghāna tasyānujaḥ krauñcam ivāvanīdhram|| 144.23||
pramāpitau vīkṣya tuhuṇḍahuṇḍau vināyakenārivināyakena|
balaṃ samastaṃ gaṇanāyakānām unmattagaṅgāpratimaṃ babhūva|| 144.24||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
catuścatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 144.141||

pañcacatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vināyakena huṇḍe ca tuhuṇḍe ca pramāpite|
gaṇeśvarāsurāṇāṃ tadyuddhaṃ saṃkulam ābabhau|| 145.1||
te naditvā yathā meghā jalamattā jalāgame|
saṃsādhayante yudhyantastvarayaiva parasparam|| 145.2||
asṛksravaiḥ suraktāṅgāḥ saṃdaṣṭadaśanacchadāḥ|
anyonyam abhisaṃjaghnuḥ śūlaśaktyṛṣṭipaṭṭiśaiḥ|| 145.3||
śaktīnāṃ kṣipyamāṇānām asīnāṃ ca nipātyatām|
śrāvyatāṃ nāmadheyānāṃ dhanuṣāṃ kūjatām api|| 145.4||
śrotrāyāsakarāñchabdān niśāmya balināṃ varaḥ|
jambho bhrātṛvadhāmarṣī praviṣṭaḥ prāmathaṃ balam|| 145.5||
vyāghrapūrvaṃ triśūlena jambho bhittvā gaṇeśvaram|
nanarda mahiṣaṃ hatvā vane vanapatiryathā|| 145.6||
nardamānasya tasyātha prathamo magapūrvakaḥ|
śiro 'abhihatya śaktyā tu śeṣān daityān pradudruve|| 145.7||
gaṇapāpi tataḥ khyātāḥ khyātavīryayaśaḥśrutāḥ|
pratīyurasurān yuddhe śarabhāḥ kuñjarāniva|| 145.8||
tato 'asuragaṇeśānāṃ saṃnipāto 'abhavanmahān|
saṃghaṭṭa iva vajrāṇāṃ saha kāñcanaparvataiḥ|| 145.9||
virocanaścāndhakaśca vavarṣaturamarṣaṇau|
śaravṛṣṭīḥ susaṃrabdhau jalavṛṣṭīrivāmbudau|| 145.10||
svayamprabheṇa tau daityau śaravarṣavisarjanau|
vimukhau saṃyugamukhe kṛtau śaravarārditau|| 145.11||
svayamprabho dānavasainyasāgaraṃ śarairanekairdhanuyantraniḥsṛtaiḥ|
saṃśoṣayaddīptamarīcimaṇḍalo yathā vivasvāñjagataḥ kṣaye 'arṇavam|| 145.12||
tato 'andhako dānavalokasārathiḥ svasārathiṃ prāha vivṛttalocanaḥ|
śukraṃ prati prāpāya sārathe māṃ sa naḥ sadā suḥkhaharo guruśca|| 145.13||
sa taṃ rathaṃ dānavayūthapāsthitaṃ tatheti ca procya sadaśvasaṃyutam|
samprāpayāmāsa payodanisvanaṃ sa yatra śukro grahasattamo dvija|| 145.14||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
pañcacatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 145.141||

ṣaṭcatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
apasṛtya tato yuddhādandhako 'asurasattamaḥ|
śukrāntikam upāgamya idam āha natānanaḥ|| 146.1||
bhagavaṃstvāṃ samāśritya vayaṃ devān sahānugān|
gaṇayāmastṛṇaistulyān sadā satyaṃ bravīmyaham|| 146.2||
kuñjarā iva siṃhānāṃ garuḍānām ivāhayaḥ|
asmākaṃ bibhyati sadā devā yuṣmatprasādataḥ|| 146.3||
durgaṃ devagaṇavyūhaṃ bhavatā pratipālitāḥ|
viviśurnirbhayā daityā hradam uṣṇārditā iva|| 146.4||
vayaṃ tvaccharaṇā bhūtvā pāṣāṇā iva niścalāḥ|
sthitvā vadhāma niḥśaṅkā brāhmaṇendrendram āhave|| 146.5||
āpadbhāvena ca vayaṃ pādau tava sukhapradau|
sadārāḥ sasutāścaiva śuśrūṣāmo divāniśam|| 146.6||
abhirakṣasva satataṃ sa nastvaccharaṇāgatān|
bhayeṣu satataṃ devān nārāyaṇa ivāparaḥ|| 146.7||
paśya huṇḍaṃ tuhuṇḍaṃ ca kujambhaṃ jambham eva ca|
pākaṃ kārtasvanaṃ caiva vipākaṃ ca mahāsuram|| 146.8||
taṃ cendradamanaṃ śūraṃ śūrāmaranipātanam|
pramathairbhīmavikrāntaiḥ krāntamṛtyuvyathādibhiḥ|| 146.9||
sūditān patitānetān hariṇairiva candanān|
yā pītvā kaṇadhūmaṃ vai sahasraṃ śaradāṃ purā|
vidyā harādvarā prāptā tasyāḥ kālo 'ayam āgataḥ|| 146.10||
atha vidyāphalaṃ tat te jīvayānasya dānavān|
paśyantu pramathāḥ sarve lokāścotphullalocanāḥ|| 146.11||
tvayā saṃjīvitān dṛṣṭvā dānavā dānavān yudhi|
sarve mṛtyubhayaṃ hitvā yotsyante pramathaiḥ saha|| 146.12||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
vidyā kila tvayā sā vai dānavānāṃ hitārthinā|| 146.13||
ārādhya devaṃ samprāptā tāṃ darśaya namastava|
ityandhakavacaḥ śrutvā sthiradhīrbhārgavo muniḥ|| 146.14||
īṣatsmitaṃ tadā kṛtvā dānavādhipam abravīt|
dānavādhipa tat satyaṃ yat tvayā preritaṃ vacaḥ|| 146.15||
vidyopārjanam etaddhi dānavānāṃ mayā kṛtam|
pītvā varṣasahasraṃ vai kaṇadhūmaṃ suduḥsaham|| 146.16||
eṣā prāptā mayā vidyā bāndhavānāṃ sukhāvahā|
etayā vidyayā so 'aham etān daityān parairhatān|| 146.17||
utthāpayiṣye sasyāni mlānānyambudharo yathā|
nirvraṇān nīrujān svasthān suptveva punarutthitān|| 146.18||
asmin muhūrte draṣṭāsi dānavān dānavādhipa|
utthitān dānavān dṛṣṭvā hatān yuddhe gaṇeśvaraiḥ|| 146.19||
vismayācca bhayāccaiva draviṣyanti gaṇeśvarāḥ|
idevam uktvā sa tadā bhārgavo dānaveśvaram|| 146.20||
ekaikaṃ daityam uddiśya vidyām āvartayat kaviḥ|
āvartamānayā tatra vudyayā brāhmaṇena ha|| 146.21||
uttasthurdānavāḥ suptāḥ śayanādiva nidrayā|
vedārthā iva cābhyastāḥ samayeneva cāmbudāḥ|| 146.22||
kālena pralayaṃ prāptau yathā vā dhūmaketavaḥ|
tathā śukreṇa te daityāḥ pramathaiḥ saṃniṣūditāḥ|| 146.23||
utthāpyamānā vibabhuryathā svasthāḥ purātanāḥ|
śukreṇojjīvitān dṛṣṭvā dānavāṃstān gaṇeśvarāḥ|| 146.24||
āścaryam etaddeveśā iti te 'anyonyam abruvan|
ujjīvitāṃstu tān dṛṣṭvā tuhuṇḍādyān mahāsurān|
vineduḥ pūrvadevāste jalamattā ivāmbudāḥ|| 146.25||
tānutthitān vīkṣya sahasraśo 'anye kuṭhāravajrāśaniśūlahastāḥ|
pradudruvuḥ śaṃkarakiṃkarāṇāṃ balaṃ samuddhūtamahārṇavābham|| 146.26||
samāgamastatra punarbabhūva gaṇāsurāṇām atibhīmanādaḥ|
yugātyate mārutavejitānāṃ yathā samudyoga ivārṇavānām|| 146.27||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe daityojjīvane
ṣaṭcatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 146.146||

saptacatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
utthāpiteṣu daityeṣu bhārgaveṇograkarmaṇā|
nedurdevāḥ sagandharvā dānavāśca sahāndhakāḥ|| 147.1||
tataḥ śaṅkharavonmiśrā māḍukānakanisvanāḥ|
babhūvuḥ siṃhanādāśca rathahastiravaiḥ saha|| 147.2||
huṇḍatuhuṇḍau jambhaśca kujambhaśca mahāsuraḥ|
śailaśūlaśilāghātairyuyudhurdevatārayaḥ|| 147.3||
pākendradamanau tau ca sa ca kārtasvano baliḥ|
mamarduḥ pramathānīkaṃ vairaṃ praticikīrṣayā|| 147.4||
teṣāṃ vegaṃ saṃnivārya pramathā api darpitāḥ|
śilātarukarāḥ sarve dānavānabhidudruvuḥ|| 147.5||
gaṇeśvarāḥ surāṇāṃ tu tasmin yuddhe 'atibhairave|
śrūyante dhanuṣāṃ śabdā rathaśabdāśca bhairavāḥ|| 147.6||
pramathānāṃ jaye saktā dānavānāṃ tathāpare|
cakruḥ kolāhalaṃ ghoraṃ pakṣavādāṃstathāmbare|| 147.7||
garjatāṃ dhāvatāṃ caiva balānāṃ samabhūt svanaḥ|
garjatāṃ dhāvatāṃ caiva samudrāṇām ivātyaye|| 147.8||
yuddhātiśayamattāśca siddhagandharvacāraṇāḥ|
neduścaivotsasarjuśca nānākusumasaṃcayān|| 147.9||
nānāvidhāni puṣpāṇi patamānāni rejire|
siddhacāraṇamuktāni nakṣatrāṇi yathātyaye|| 147.10||
devagandharvatūryāṇi prasasvanuranekśaḥ|
yuddhasaṃsaktabhāvānāṃ viremuśca punaḥ punaḥ|| 147.11||
vināyakena smṛtvā tu jambho yudhi parābhavam|
taṃ sakrodho 'abhidudrāva gajaṃ gaja ivāparaḥ|| 147.12||
tam āpatantaṃ dṛṣṭvā tu dānavaṃ jambham āhave|
siṃho gajam iva kruddho rurudhe sa vināyakaḥ|| 147.13||
airāvatakaraprakhyaṃ karaṃ karinibhānanaḥ|
utkṣipya dānavaṃ yuddhe tatāḍa sa vināyakaḥ|| 147.14||
kumbhayorantare taṃ tu jambho dānavakuñjaraḥ|
bibheda śaramukhyena yathā siddho 'arkamaṇḍalam|| 147.15||
kumbhayorantare tasya nimamajja sa vai śaraḥ|
śṛṅgayoracalendrasya taḍitvāniva cāmnudaḥ|| 147.16||
sa śarāroṣitamanā vidhūya saśiraḥkaram|
karagreṇa mahādaityam ānamyāhatya so 'anadat|| 147.17||
praspandamāno jambhastu vināyakakarāhataḥ|
vināyakaṃ śarairugrairavatastāra roṣitaḥ|| 147.18||
śalabhā iva kedāraṃ bhramarā iva pādapam|
jambheṣavastadā devaṃ viviśuste vināyakam|| 147.19||
rudhiraṃ kṣaramāṇāste trivittrairdāritānanās|
śarā vināyake rejuḥ sarpā merum ivāśritāḥ|| 147.20||
sa jambhabāṇairatibhinnagātraḥ kumbhāsrutāvāplutaraktanetraḥ|
dhunvan karāgraṃ ca śiraśca devo dudrāva jambhaṃ tṛṣito yathāmbhaḥ|| 147.21||
sa taṃ karāgreṇa dṛḍhaṃ dṛḍhena muhuḥ samāhatya muhurvinadya|
rathaṃ gṛhītvā balavāṃstadājau cikṣepa sāśvadhvajaśastracakram|| 147.22||
soddhūtabhagnātipatākaketuścyutāsiśaktyṛṣṭisahasrabāṇaḥ|
rathaḥ papātāsuranandanasya manorathastīvra ivādhanasya|| 147.23||
patīṣyamāṇaṃ tu rathaṃ vihāya prahrādirindrāmbudharaprabhāvaḥ|
sthito 'ambare śaktidharo rarāja sthito 'ambare śaktidharo yathaiva|| 147.24||
sa tāṃ saghaṇṭāṃ kanakāvadātāṃ kṛśānulekhām iva dīpyamānām|
vināyakāyāsurarājaputraścikṣepa śaktiṃ samudīrṇaśaktiḥ|| 147.25||
sā khāt patantī bhujagāṅganeva śastrāṅganā prajvalamānavaktrā|
śarāhatā viṭpatinā papāta śaktiryathāgryā puruṣe hatāśe|| 147.26||
āścaryabhūte pramathāsurāṇāṃ tasmiṃstathā vartati yuddhayajñe|
amarṣito bhārgavakarma dṛṣṭvā śilādaputro 'abhyagamanmaheśam|| 147.27||
jayeti soktvā jayayonim ugram uvāca nandī kanakāvadātam|
gaṇeśvarāṇāṃ raṇakarma deva devaiḥ sahendrairapi duṣkaraṃ yat|| 147.28||
tadbhārgaveṇādya kṛtaṃ vṛthā naḥ saṃjīvayānena hi dānavendrān|
ete hi te dānavayūthapālā yamālayādadya punarnivṛttāḥ|| 147.29||
vidrāvayantaḥ pramathāṃścaranti nāgānivājau śarabhāḥ sadarpāḥ|
yadi hyasau daityavarān nirastānujjīvayatyeva punaḥ sadaiva|| 147.30||
jayaḥ kuto vai bhavitā maheśa gaṇeśvarāṇāṃ kuta eva śāntiḥ|
vakrasthitaścaiṣa na caiṣa vadhyo 'ayudhyamāno vṛṣavāha śukraḥ|| 147.31||
naivābhināśo 'asti tava prasādāddhataṃ ca taṃ tvaṃ kuruṣe prasādam|
bhavet taveśāna mataṃ sa vadhyo yathā jayaste samare 'aniśaṃ syāt|
tathā kuruṣvottamabuddhibuddha na te maheśāna samo 'asti buddhyā|| 147.32||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ityevam uktaḥ pramatheśvareṇa nandīśvareṇeśvaradevadevaḥ|
uvāca devaḥ prahasaṃstadānīṃ sa nandinaṃ sarvagaṇeśanāyakam|| 147.33||
nandin prayāhi tvarito 'atimātraṃ dvijendrabandhuṃ ditinandanānām|
madhyāt samutpāṭya tam ānayasva yathopahāraṃ dhanavān namuṣyaḥ|| 147.34||
sa evam ukto vṛṣabhadhvajena vṛṣadhvajo vai vṛṣasiṃhanādaḥ|
jagāma tūrṇaṃ pravigāhya senāṃ yatrābhavadbhārgavavaṃśadīpaḥ|| 147.35||
taṃ rakṣamāṇaṃ ditinandanaistaiḥ pāśāsivṛkṣopalaśūlahastaiḥ|
vikṣobhya daityān vṛṣarāḍjahāra śukraṃ sa nandī śarabho yathebham|| 147.36||
srastāmbaraṃ taṃ cyutabhūṣaṇaṃ ca vimuktakeśaṃ ripuṇā gṛhītam|
vimokṣayiṣyanta ivābhyadhāvan surārayaḥ siṃharavān sṛjantaḥ|| 147.37||
te vajraśūleṣuparaśvadhānāṃ sacakradaṇḍopalakampanānām(?)|
nandīśvarasyopari dānavendrā varṣaṃ vavarṣurjaladā ivogrāḥ|| 147.38||
sa bhārgavaṃ prāpya gaṇādhipāgryo vaktrāgninā śastraśatāni dagdhvā|
āyāt sa śukraṃ tu kare gṛhītvā nandīśvaro dānavayūthapālam|| 147.39||
teṣāṃ ca teṣāṃ ca tato babhūva pramuktaśastrāstrasubhīmapātaḥ|
jahīti gṛhṇeti ca vādināṃ vai mahāhavo devamanaḥpratoṣaḥ|| 147.40||
tenāntareṇaitya bhavasya pārśvaṃ nandīśvaraḥ krodhavivarṇanetraḥ|
ayaṃ sa śukro bhagavannitīśe nivedayāmāsa bhavāya śīghram|| 147.41||
jagrāha śukraṃ sa ca devadevo yathopahāraṃ śucinā pradattam|
vaktrasthitaṃ śukram ariṃ jagāra na kiṃciduktvā sa hi bhūtagoptā|| 147.42||
tataḥ punardānavadaityasainyaṃ gaṇeśvarāstasya tadā vijaghnuḥ|| 147.43||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe bhārgavaharaṇe
saptacatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 147.147||

aṣṭacatvāriṃśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śukre 'atha śukrapatinā gīrṇe 'anneva bhujaṅginā|
babhūvurdānavāḥ sarve daridrā iva niṣkriyāḥ|| 148.1||
viśarīrā yathā jīvā garuḍā virayā iva|
vihastā iva mātaṅgā viśṛṅgā iva govṛṣāḥ|| 148.2||
nirviṣā iva nāgendrā nirvidyā iva ca dvijāḥ|
sāgarā iva nistoyā vivegā iva mārutāḥ|| 148.3||
payodā iva niḥśabdā viśikhā iva cāgnayaḥ|
gatotsavā va divasā vipuṣpā iva pādapāḥ|| 148.4||
hariṇā iva saṃtrastā vipakṣā iva pakṣiṇaḥ|
grahā iva praśāntābhā grāhā iva jaloddhṛtāḥ|| 148.5||
nandināpahṛte śukre gīrṇe cāpi kapardinā|
dānavā jajñire śūrā dīnamānaparākramāḥ|| 148.6||
vaimanasyaṃ paraṃ prāpto dānavānāṃ raṇe 'andhakaḥ|
uvāca meghaninadaḥ saṃyugasthaḥ sa dānavaḥ|| 148.7||
vikramya nandinā śukraṃ nayatā nayināṃ varam|
hṛtāni no 'adya sarveṣāṃ jīvitāni na saṃśayaḥ|| 148.8||
pramathairnihatān daityān kaḥ punarjīvayiṣyati|
bhārgavaṃ tam ṛte śukraṃ ko 'anyo no dhārayiṣyati|| 148.9||
dhairyaṃ ca vikramastejaḥ sattvaṃ vīryaṃ balaṃ dhṛtiḥ|
śatrubhirno hṛtaṃ sarvaṃ deve śukre 'apavāhite|| 148.10||
bhārgave 'apahṛte deve mamāpi vyathitaṃ manaḥ|
na tvahaṃ saṃyugaṃ jahyāṃ pramathaiḥ samabhidrutaḥ|| 148.11||
saṃstambhayata mā bhaiṣṭa yudhyadhvam aribhiḥ saha|
sūdayiṣyāmyahaṃ sarvān pramathān saha nandinā|| 148.12||
adyaitān vivaśān kṛtvā hatvā ca tridaśānapi|
bhārgavaṃ mokṣayiṣyāmi pañjarasthaṃ yathā harim|| 148.13||
sa cāpi yogī yogena yadi nāma svayaṃ prabhuḥ|
śarīrānniṣkramet tasya asmākaṃ śeṣapālinaḥ|| 148.14||
ityandhakavacaḥ śrutvā dānavā meghanardanāḥ|
pramathānardayāmāsurmartavyakṛtaniścayāḥ|| 148.15||
tatra ṣāṇāśivajraughaiḥ kaṭaṅkaṭaśilopalaiḥ|
anyonyam avakṛntantaste cakruḥ kadanaṃ mahat|| 148.16||
kārmukāṇāṃ vikṛṣṭānāṃ visṛṣṭānāṃ ca patriṇām|
nipātyatām asīnāṃ ca śabdo 'abhūdbhṛśadāruṇaḥ|| 148.17||
bhagnadhvajapatākāni kṣīṇapraharaṇāni ca|
rudhirāsrāvacitrāṇi vraṇākusumitāni ca|| 148.18||
pipāsitāni śrāntāni hatavājigajāni ca|
samudrāmbarakalpāni balāni āsan samantataḥ|| 148.19||
atha bhūyo gajendreṇa caturdantena garjatā|
añjanācalakalpena añjanadvipavarcasā|| 148.20||
satūṇīrapatākena aṅkuśāroṣitena ca|
jambho dānavaśārdūlaḥ abhidudrāva nandinam|| 148.21||
gajaskandhagato daityo babhau jambhaḥ satomaraḥ|
kṛṣṇāparvataśṛṅgasthaḥ sabalāka ivāmbudaḥ|| 148.22||
stabdhalāṅgūladṛkkarṇaḥ prasāritamahākaraḥ|
codito dānavendreṇa samadhāvanmahāgajaḥ|| 148.23||
yugānte 'arṇavavātasya anaupamyo yathā javaḥ|
anaupamyastathā tasya javo nāgasya dhāvataḥ|| 148.24||
turaṅgā ye ca mātaṅgāḥ pramathā ye ca dānavāḥ|
tasya mārgādapakrāntā mṛtyoriva yathā narāḥ|| 148.25||
taṃ mattanāgaṃ dhāvantaṃ nadantam iva nīradam|
vārayāmāsa balavān vikramya sa vināyakaḥ|| 148.26||
sa taṃ devavaro dantī kariṇaṃ parvatopamam|
prakīrṇena karāgreṇa pramukhe 'abhijaghāna ha|| 148.27||
vināyakenābhihato nāyakaḥ sarvahastinām|
sa rujā ghorayā nunno muhūrtam abhavajjaḍaḥ|| 148.28||
athāśvasya ca viśramya saṃvartyātmakaraṃ karī|
vināyakam urodeśe tāḍayāmāsa nardayan|| 148.29||
sa vindhyakūṭakalpena tena nāgena tāḍitaḥ|
padāt padaṃ na calito mahāsattvo vināyakaḥ|| 148.30||
nāsayā sa gṛhītvā taṃ nāsāyāṃ dānavadvipam|
ākṣipya pātayāmāsa girivarṣmā vināyakaḥ|| 148.31||
sa siṃha iva siṃhena vanamadhye nipātitaḥ|
rarāsa visphuran nāgo megho vāyvāhato yathā|| 148.32||
taṃ nāgaṃ pātayānaṃ tu nāgavaktram asṛksravam|
bibheda tomareṇāśu kareṇārka ivāmbudam|| 148.33||
mocayantaṃ tu caraṇau grīvāyāṃ dānavottamam|
tenaiva tomareṇātha ājaghāna vināyakaḥ|| 148.34||
sa suprahārābhihato gajavaktreṇa dānavaḥ|
cakṣāra rudhiraṃ jambho nirjharāmbho giriryathā|| 148.35||
punaścāsya vadhākāṅkṣī asiṃ jagrāha vīryavān|
tasyodyatāsernadataścicchitsorjambhakandharām|| 148.36||
asiṃ kujambhaściccheda garuḍaḥ pannagaṃ yathā|
taṃ cāpi suvikṛṣṭena śareṇāsṛgbhujā tadā|| 148.37||
kujambho hyahanadbāhau vajreṇendra ivācalam|
sa dṛḍhābhihatastena ghūrṇitaḥ sālavṛkṣavat|| 148.38||
kujambham abhidudrāva kesarī kuñjaraṃ yathā|
samucchritakaro devastaṃ dānavam abhidravan|| 148.39||
airāvata ivābhāti balodvṛtto vināyakaḥ|
vyaṃsastaṃ dhāvamānaṃ tu kujambhavadhakāṅkṣiṇam|| 148.40||
vavāra sa gato 'aṃsena pātayāmāsa taṃ kṣitau|
vyaṃsam aṃsena hatvā tu nāgavaktro mahābalaḥ|| 148.41||
kujambhasyāntikaṃ prāpa siṃhasya śarabho yathā|
kujambhastasya bhittvā tu śareṇa karam udyatam|| 148.42||
gadayābhyahananmūrdhni mudgareṇa ca cakṣasi|
tribhiḥ prahāraiḥ sa babhau śoṇitākto vināyakaḥ|| 148.43||
dharāyāṃ nāsayādāya kujambhaṃ tu vināyakaḥ|
pracikṣepa mahāvīryo yathā bhūtabaliṃ naraḥ|| 148.44||
kujambhe mandaraprakhye vināyakabhujerite|
cakrudhurdānavāḥ sarve te 'ardayaṃśca vināyakam|| 148.45||
so 'ardito dānavaśatairnānāyudhavitakṣitaḥ|
cacāra devo daityeṣu pṛṣateṣu yathā hariḥ|| 148.46||
sa dantaiścaraṇaiścāpi śuṇḍayātatayāpi ca|
mamarda dānavān kruddhaḥ kuñjaro naḍvalāniva|| 148.47||
tato gaṇeśā hyapi vīkṣya dānavairvināyakaṃ śastraśataiḥ parikṣatam|
gṛhītaśastrā gajasiṃhavikramā vimuktarāvāḥ śataśo 'abhidudruvuḥ|| 148.48||
tataḥ punaḥ śastrasahasravejitaṃ śarāsiśaktyṛṣṭinipātaduḥsaham|
gaṇāsurāṇām asunāśanaṃ mahadbabhūva yuddhaṃ hatavājikuñjaram|| 148.49||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
aṣṭacatvāriṃśottaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 148.148||

ūnapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
nigīrṇo brāhmaṇaḥ so 'atha candrāvayavadhāriṇā|
kiṃ cakre koṣṭhagastasya devadevasya bhārgavaḥ|| 149.1||
kathaṃ ca tapasāṃ śreṣṭho yogī yogena sa dvijaḥ|
na niḥsṛto yogabalāddevadehānmahātapāḥ|| 149.2||
andhakaścāsuraśreṣṭhaḥ sa tadā bhārgavaṃ vinā|
cakāra katham āvāpaṃ gaṇeśaiḥ samabhidrutaḥ|| 149.3||
etanme sarvam akhilaṃ khelavedavidāṃ vara|
kathayasva na me tṛptiḥ śṛṇvānasyeśaceṣṭitam|| 149.4||
sūta uvāca|
athaivaṃ pṛcchatastasya vyāsasya munisattamaḥ|
sanatkumāro 'akathayacchukrasyātha viceṣṭitam|| 149.5||
sanatkumāra uvācva|
nigīrṇe bhārgave tena bhūtomādevabandhunā|
andhako niṣprabho jajñe ghanaruddho yathā raviḥ|| 149.6||
dṛṣṭvā svasainyaṃ pramathairbhajyamānaṃ punaḥ punaḥ|
dudrāva ratham āsthāya svayam evāndhako gaṇān|| 149.7||
śaravajraprahāraistairvajrāghātairddharā iva(?)|
pramathāḥ petira vanyāṃ nistoyā iva toyadāḥ|| 149.8||
kroḍeṣūrukapoleṣu pṛṣṭhabāhūdareṣu ca|
ruruvurbāṇanirbhinnāḥ pramathāḥ kuñjarā yathā|| 149.9||
yāntam āyāntam aprāptaṃ prāptaṃ dūrastham eva ca|
apaśyadyaṃ yatastaṃ taṃ nirbibheda śarairbhṛśam|| 149.10||
bibheda śatam ekena śatena ca śataṃ punaḥ|
sahasraṃ ca sahasreṇa koṭiṃ koṭyā tathaiva ca|| 149.11||
dhvajāḥ patākāśchitrāṇi vaijayantyo 'aṅkuśāḥ kuthāḥ|
cāmarāṇi kirīṭāni kuṇḍalānyambarāṇi ca|| 149.12||
pramathānāṃ bale yacca kampate dhāvate 'api vā|
tat sarvaṃ cicchide tūrṇaṃ śarairandhakadānavaḥ|| 149.13||
visphuliṅgān yathaivāgnirdhārāsārān yathāmbudaḥ|
sindhurājo yathodgārān karāniva divākaraḥ|| 149.14||
nādān siṃhā ivāraṇye sīkarāniva kuñjarāḥ|
mumoca bāṇāṃstīkṣṇāgrān parasainyavimardanān|| 149.15||
andhake yudhyamāne tu niścayenaurottame|
asurā apyayudhyanta niścayenāndhakādanu|| 149.16||
nivātakavacā ye te anyonyasadṛśā bhṛśam|
cakruste bahavo yuddhaṃ rudraiśca bahubhiḥ saha|| 149.17||
kāleyāḥ ṣaṣṭisāhasrāḥ kālakalpā mahāsurāḥ|
bāhujaiḥ ṣaṣṭisāhasraiḥ pramathairyuyudhuḥ saha|| 149.18||
prahrādaścānuhrādaśca saṃhrādaḥ śinibāṣkalau|
virocano balirbāṇaḥ kujambho 'athāvaniṃjayaḥ|| 149.19||
añjakaḥ kālanemiśca namucirvyaṃsa eva ca|
ekādaśaite prakhyātā ekādaśaraviprabhāḥ|| 149.20||
ekādaśaiva pramathānardayan kalahaiṣiṇaḥ|
prabhāmayaṃ vīrabhadraṃ viṭpatiṃ piṅgalaṃ tathā|| 149.21||
vegapaṃ pavanādaṃ ca somārkāpyāyanāvapi|
saṃvarttakānalaṃ caiva pāvakāpyāyanāvapi (?)|| 149.22||
yakṣo 'annadaśca balavān vidyutkeśaśca rākṣasaḥ|
prahrādapramukhairetairdānavairdevapuṅgavāḥ|| 149.23||
vihastaśastrakavacāvṛtāḥ śastraśatācitāḥ|
dvārapālāśca rudrāṇāṃ rudrāṇāṃ ye ca sūnavaḥ|| 149.24||
skandapāriṣadā ye ca ye ca śaktigaṇeśvarāḥ|
te danostanayaiḥ sārdhaṃ danoḥ putrānvayāśca ye|
cakruḥ kṛtāntasadṛśāḥ kalahaṃ kalahapraiyāḥ|| 149.25||
tasmiṃstathā vartati samprahāre viśīrṇahārābharaṇasragastraiḥ|
vyāviddhavastrā vikasatsunetrā neduḥ surāḥ siddhagaṇāśca khasthāḥ|| 149.26||
iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe
ūnapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 149.149||

pañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
māyāvīryaṃ ca vīryaṃ ca andhakasyāmaradviṣaḥ|
sṛṣṭaṃ bhagavatā samyagdevarūpanimittajam|| 150.1||
nigīrṇo yasya devena śarīre bhārgavo muniḥ|
kathaṃ tu kṛtavāṃstatra devadevaśarīragaḥ|| 150.2||
kathaṃ ca tapaso vīryādyogavīryācca sa dvijaḥ|
śvetābhrādiva vai candro niḥsṛto bhṛgunandanaḥ|| 150.3||
etat kautūhalaṃ jātaṃ mamādya munisattama|
kathayeśānacaritaṃ bhārgavasya ca dhīmataḥ|| 150.4||
sūta uvāca|
sa evam ukto vyāsena padmagarbhasutaḥ prabhuḥ|
sanatkumāro 'akathayacchivācchukrasya nirgamam|| 150.5||
dehe tasya tadā śambhoḥ śukro vinihatadyutiḥ|
chidrānveṣī bhramanneva aniketo yathānilaḥ|| 150.6||
sa lokānagnivarṇābhān rudrakoṭiśatairvṛtān|
rudrakanyāvicaritān rudradehe 'abhyapaśyata|| 150.7||
kundenduśaṅkhavarṇānāṃ daṃṣṭriṇāṃ nakhinām api|
dīrghalāṅgūlajuṣṭānāṃ sadarpāṇāṃ kṣamāvatām|| 150.8||
jvalanaprabhakeśānāṃ nandyāvartakadhāriṇām|
kiṃśukaprabhajihvānāṃ kailāsagirivarṣmaṇām|| 150.9||
agnibandhanabaddhānāṃ siṃhānāṃ bhīmarūpiṇām|
sahasraṃ dadṛśe dehe devadevasya bhārgavaḥ|| 150.10||
surāṃśca sendrān sādityān sāpsarogaṇamānavān|
gaṇeśāsurayuddhaṃ ca so 'apaśyaddharadehagaḥ|| 150.11||
varṣāṇāṃ tu śataṃ kakṣau bhramamāṇo bhavasya saḥ|
na tasya dadṛśe chidraṃ śuceriva yathā kaliḥ|| 150.12||
yogam apyasya saiśvaryam aṇimādiguṇānvitam|
prajahāra mahādevo manovāgyatacetasaḥ|| 150.13||
atha śabdo mahān āsīt pramathāsurasainyayoḥ|
taṃ śrutvā śabdam āvigno bhārgavaḥ pratibodhitaḥ|| 150.14||
so 'antargata umābharturbrāhmaṇastapasaidhitaḥ|
tuṣṭāveṣṭaiḥ stavairdevaṃ somaṃ somavibhūṣaṇam|| 150.15||
āpadbhāvaṃ prapannasya tasya devena śūlinā|
liṅgena niṣkamasveti prasādābhyudayaḥ kṛtaḥ|| 150.16||
sūkṣmarūpastato bhūtvā sa śukro munisattamaḥ|
śukravan niḥsṛto liṅgāddevadevasya dhīmataḥ|| 150.17||
śakravanniḥsṛto yasmācchiśnādbhārgavanandanaḥ|
tasmācchukra iti khyātiṃ gato gatimatāṃ varaḥ|| 150.18||
vandamānaśca tenoktaḥ payodapatiketunā|
śukravanniḥsṛto me 'adya yasmāt tvaṃ bhṛgunandana|| 150.19||
karmaṇā tena śukro 'asi mama putraśca gamyatām|
ityevam ukto devena śukro 'arkasadṛśadyutiḥ|| 150.20||
viveśa dānavānīkaṃ meghānīkaṃ śaśī yathā|
taṃ dṛṣṭvā candrasaṃkāśaṃ candrodayanibhodayam|| 150.21||
candrodaye yathā nR̥ṇāṃ prītirāsīt suradviṣām|
te dṛṣṭvā danudaiteyāḥ śukraṃ candrasamaprabham|| 150.22||
sarve siṃharavāṃścakruḥ samprahṛṣṭā yuyutsavaḥ|
nihatā dānavā ye tu pramathairjitakāśibhiḥ|| 150.23||
tān āgatān mṛtyumukhān menire bhārgavāgamāt|
vavandustaṃ nananduśca praseduśca mahāsurāḥ|| 150.24||
śukrodayamudaṃ lebhe sa dānavamahārṇavaḥ|
yathā candrodaye nityaṃ sāgaro rākṣasairyutaḥ|| 150.25||
atha śākho viśākhaśca chāgavaktraścaturmukhaḥ|
nandī ca somanandī ca nandiṣeṇaśca vīryavān|| 150.26|
ghaṇṭākarṇaḥ śaṅkukarṇaḥ kuṇḍodaramahodarau|
viṣpatirvīrabhadraśca sa ca devaḥ prabhāmayaḥ|| 150.27||
saṃvartakānalorvau ca yaśodīpto vibhākaraḥ|
vegapaśca śikhaṇḍī ca tāmracūḍaśca kukkuṭaḥ|| 150.28||
annadaḥ piṅgalo yakṣaḥ piṅgalaśca vaṭuḥ paṭuḥ|
vidyutkeśaḥ sukeśaśca rākṣasau cāparājitau|| 150.29||
ete cānye ca gaṇapā lokapālasamatviṣaḥ|
viviśurdānavānīkaṃ śukrodayasamuddhatam|| 150.30||
atha vāditraśabdāstu suṃhanādaravaiḥ saha|
babhūvuḥ senayorugrāḥ sarvabhūtaprakampanāḥ|| 150.31||
tataḥ praharaṇairghoraistuṇḍanirvāpitaistalaiḥ|
parasparaṃ samāsādya nirjaghnuste parasparam|| 150.32||
nandīśvaraṃ puraskṛtya kārttikeyaṃ ca ṣaṇmukham|
mṛdranti pramathā daityān sarpāṃstārkṣya ivāhave|| 150.33||
asipātāvalūnāgrā muśalāhatamastakāḥ|
dānavāḥ śerate bhūmau vajrabhinnā ivācalāḥ|| 150.34||
śaranirbhinnanirbhagnāḥ sambhagnoruprabāhavaḥ|
rirṅguḥ samare daityāḥ sarpāstārkṣyārditā iva|| 150.35||
bhagnatrikorujaghanā ghanabāṇāvapīḍitāḥ|
daityā viniṣṭananti ārttā yoyapūrṇā ivāmbudāḥ|| 150.36||
tasmin gaṇapadaityānāṃ mathane bhṛśadāruṇe|
babhūva pūrṇā daityānāṃ dharā dyauriva nīradaiḥ|| 150.37||
kirīṭairmukuṭairhārairvalayābharaṇāṅgadaiḥ|
pārihāryaiḥ sa keyūraiḥ śroṇīsūtraiḥ sakuṇḍalaiḥ|| 150.38||
śirastrairmaṇibhiḥ śubhrairgraiveyairapi suprabhaiḥ|
sragdāmaiścārukusumairnetrai ratnāgravāhubhiḥ|| 150.39||
astraiḥ śastraiśca vastraiśca chatraiścendusamaprabhaiḥ|
raktakuṅkumacitrāṅgī nānābharaṇabhūṣaṇā|| 150.40||
dhanāḍhyā strīrivābhāti tatra tatra raṇāvaniḥ|
siṃhānām iva dṛptānāṃ hastinām api vā yathā|| 150.41||
utsāho 'abhūdgaṇeśānāṃ dānavān sampramardatām|
te hanyamānāśaraṇā bhayārttāḥ śaraṇārthinaḥ|| 150.42||
pramathairanubaddhāśca dānavāḥ sāgaraṃ śritāḥ|
dṛṣṭvā tadrecitaṃ sainyaṃ dānavaiḥ pramathārditaiḥ|| 150.43||
praviṣṭeṣu ca daityeṣu sāgaraṃ makarālayam|
bhārgavaḥ sumahātejā yathāgniriva mūrchitaḥ|| 150.44||
sa samudrālayān daityāñchaśāpa kupito bhṛśam|
yasmāt sahāyānutsṛjya māṃ cāpi pitṛvaddhitam|| 150.45||
prāṇatrāṇārtham abalāḥ praviṣṭāḥ stha payonidhim|
tasmāt tatraiva nirhrīkā mama śāpaparikṣatāḥ|| 150.46||
mīnabhāvam anuprāptā jātājātā bhaviṣyatha|
yāvallokā bhaviṣyanti parvatāśca sasāgarāḥ|| 150.47||
tāvadyūyaṃ jale matsyā bhaviṣyatha jalecarāḥ|
naramāṃsāśanāḥ pāpā narabhakṣyā bhaviṣyatha|| 150.48||
kṣapayiṣyatha macchāpaṃ varṣakoṭīśatānyuta|
iti śāpahatāñcheṣān kṛtvārṇavajalaukasaḥ|
virarāma mahātejāḥ śukraścandrasamadyutiḥ|| 150.49||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataste vārdhitoyeṣu guruśāpahatāsurāḥ|
sāyudhāḥ satanutrāśca dṛśyante daṃśitāśca ha|| 150.50||
andhakaṃ tu tataḥ śukraḥ śukrāribhayavihvalam|
uvāca pāṇinā spṛśya jīvayanniva taṃ girā|| 150.51||
mā bhaistvaṃ dānavaśreṣṭha pratiyudhyasva śatruṣu|
ahaṃ tvāṃ dhārayiṣyāmi āhāra iva jīvitam|| 150.52||
ityevam uktaḥ śukreṇa so 'andhako dānaveśvaraḥ|
evam etaditi procya rurodha pramathān raṇe|| 150.53||
tataḥ praviṣṭeṣvasureṣu sāgaraṃ nihanyamāneṣu ca śaṅkarānugaiḥ|
dadhāra sarvān pramathāṃstadāndhako nadīnadān bhūrijalo yathārṇavaḥ|| 150.54||
sa nandinaṃ dvādaśabhiḥ parābhinat tadāndhakaḥ pañcabhireva cāgnijam|
viśākaśākhau daśabhiḥ śatena ca sa naigameṣaṃ pratutoda dānavaḥ|| 150.55||
sa vīrabhadraṃ ca tathā ca viṭpatiṃ prabhāmayaṃ yakṣavaraṃ ca piṅgalam|
bibheda bāṇaistapanīyabhūṣaṇairyathāṅkuśāgrairiva hastipo gajam|| 150.56||
na so 'asti tasmin purato na pṛṣṭhato hayo gajo vā pramatho 'athavetaraḥ|
śarān na yo dhārayate 'andhakeritān pradīptakālānalasūryasannibhān|| 150.57||
vivṛścitāścandanavadgaṇeśvarā bhujodare vakṣasi mūrdhni cāsakṛt|
nirudyamāstasthuramitranandanā yathā gajāḥ pañjarabandhabandhanāḥ|| 150.58||
tato 'asuraiḥ siṃharavāstadā kṛtāḥ saśaṅkhabherīśatadundubhotkaṭāḥ|
punaśca yuddhaṃ prababhau bhayānakaṃ gaṇeśvarāṇāṃ saha dānaveśvaraiḥ|| 150.59||
|| iti skandapurāṇe gaṇayuddhe 'asuraśāpe
pañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 150.150||

ekapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
vartamāne 'andhake yuddhe vidravatsu gaṇeṣu ca|
tridaśādhipatiṃ śakram ityuvāca pitāmahaḥ|| 151.1||
vimukhān paśya bhadraṃ te pramathānamarādhipa|
kālyamānān raṇe ghorairdānavairandhakena ca|| 151.2||
nihatān nihatāneṣa pramathairdānavān yudhi|
śukra ujjīvayan āste sasyāni jalado yathā|| 151.3||
asau vikṛṣṭacāpaśca sendrāyudhaghanopamaḥ|
sṛjatīṣumayaṃ varṣam andhakaḥ kṣapayan ripūn|| 151.4||
pramathābhyardanaṃ hyetadahitaṃ hyayaśaskaram|
kṣamamāṇā hyatiṣṭhadhvaṃ kasmādetat parājayam|| 151.5||
jitvā hyeṣa gaṇān sarvānandhako dānaveśvaraḥ|
asmākam api mūlāni nirmūlāni kariṣyati|| 151.6||
tadyāvadeṣa no bāṇaiḥ pramathān nayati kṣayam|
tāvadeva vayaṃ pārṣṇiṃ gṛhṇāma kṛttivāsasaḥ|| 151.7||
evaṃ tava ca kāryārthaḥ setsyate devatādhipa|
rudrasya ca kṛtaṃ hyevaṃ bhaviṣyati mahat priyam|| 151.8||
svayambhuvacanaṃ śrutvā balavṛtanibarhaṇaḥ|
yuktam etaditi procya surān surapatirjagau|| 151.9||
gṛhītavarmaśastrāstrāḥ śīghraṃ śighraparākramāḥ|
sāhāyyaṃ karavāmādya gaṇānāṃ yudhyatāṃ raṇe|| 151.10||
tato nārāyaṇānantau narendrau candra eva ca|
svayambhuranalo vāyuḥ sūryo dhamada eva ca|| 151.11||
pūṣāryamā bhago mitro yamaśca ravinandanaḥ|
aṃśastvaṣṭā jayaścaiva jayantaścaiva śakrajaḥ|| 151.12||
maruto vasavaḥ sādhyāstathāśvigarudoragāḥ|
tuṣitāścaiva lekhāśca viśvedevāśca guhyakāḥ|| 151.13||
gandharvāścaiva yakṣāśca ye cānye devapakṣiṇaḥ|
te sarve vātaran yuddhe hantukāmāstathāndhakam|| 151.14||
atha dundubhiśabdāśca siṃhanādāśca bhairavāḥ|
babhūvurdevasainyeṣu pramathānāṃ priyaṃkarāḥ|| 151.15||
devaiḥ patadbhistat sainyaṃ dānavānāṃ viloḍitam|
prabhūtamīnaṃ kṣīṇāmbu rājahaṃsairyathā saraḥ|| 151.16||
tato halahalāśabdaḥ saṃjajñe 'atīvabhairavaḥ|
devatādhyuṣite sainye dānavānāṃ samākule|| 151.17||
sāmudram ambhastimibhirghanairiva yathā nabhaḥ|
kaphapittairyathā deho garuḍairbhogino yathā|| 151.18||
tathā tadandhakabalaṃ balena tridivaukasām|
muhūrtena kṛtaṃ sarvaṃ vihastakavacadhvajam|| 151.19||
ekataḥ sendrakairdevairekataśca gaṇeśvaraiḥ|
janyate dānavānīkam ajā vṛkaśatairiva|| 151.20||
vajrodyatakaro devo devānāṃ devapuṅgavaḥ|
.okāra iva vedānāṃ teṣām āsīt puraḥsaraḥ|| 151.21||
vajrāstrapāvakenendro dadāha samare ripūn|
duritāni tu sarvāṇi prāyaścittānalo yathā|| 151.22||
devaiśca pramathaiścaiva hanyamāne bale 'andhakaḥ|
uavāca krodharāgāndho dānavān dānavādhipaḥ|| 151.23||
utpādya vairaṃ rudreṇa sarvalokābhirakṣaṇā|
na śakyaṃ pramathāñjetum anirviṇṇaiḥ sahāmarān|| 151.24||
maraṇācca na bhetavyaṃ yudhyadhvaṃ daityadānavāḥ|
bhārgavastiṣṭhati hyeṣa yo naḥ saṃjīvayiṣyati|| 151.25||
tat prāṇeṣvadayanto vai yūyaṃ devagaṇeśvarān|
yathābalaṃ yathotsāhaṃ vārayadhvam aśaṅkitāḥ|| 151.26||
māyābhiretān bahvībhirgūḍābhirgūḍharūpiṇaḥ|
nivārayata yuddhena sarvān devān samāgatān|| 151.27||
ityuktā -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- cakrurghorāṇi kalpānte nīradā iva|| 151.28||
dhanuḥśabdān prakurvāṇāḥ siṃhanādaravāṃstathā|
dudruvurdānavā devānandhakena pracoditāḥ|| 151.29||
vikṛṣya tu mahācāpaṃ sāgarāmbudanardanaḥ|
rudram uddiśya vegena sasārāndhakadānavaḥ|| 151.30||
taṃ dānavednraṃ durvāraṃ dhāvamāna-- -- -- --|
vārayāmāsa śailādrirdharmacittam ivāśubham|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 151.31||
sa nandinaṃ tribhirbāṇairjvalanādityasannibhaiḥ|
nirbibhedāndhakaḥ krodhādbāhumadhye nipīḍayan|| 151.32||
gāḍhaṃ vidāritastena dānavena gaṇeśvaraḥ|
saṃjughūrṇa tadā nandī vāyununno yathādrumaḥ|| 151.33||
ghūrṇamāno babhau nandī mṛṣṭakuṇḍalabhūṣaṇaḥ|
calatpallavapuṣpāḍhyo yathāśokatarustathā|| 151.34||
tataścirāt samāśvasya suyaśāḥ suyaśāpatiḥ|
vajram ūrjitam utkṣipya so 'andhakāya sasarja ha|| 151.35||
tat pāvakaraviprakhyaṃ vajram āgatam ūrjitam|
vyaṣṭambhayata bāṇaughairandhakaḥ prajahāsa ca|| 151.36||
hasatastasya netrābhyāṃ subhrūbhyām aśrubindavaḥ|
nyasravanta yathārkasya kiraṇā dīptamaṇḍalāt|| 151.37||
bhūtarājastatotpāṭya drumaṃ vyākulapallavam|
hato 'asi he 'andhaketyuktvā sasarja ca jagarja ca|| 151.38||
taṃ dhāvamānam ākāśe tarumārutavījitāḥ|
anuvrajanti bhramarā mitraṃ vyasanagaṃ yathā|| 151.39||
tam apyasyāndhako bāṇaiścārukāñcanabhūṣaṇaiḥ|
cakarta dhartā lokānāṃ ditigarbhaṃ yathāhihā|| 151.40||
vṛkṣe kṛtte tato nandī samṛgavyālapannagam|
mandarāgraṃ samutpāṭya dudrāvāndhakam āhave|| 151.41||
girikūṭaṃ tu taṃ nandī girikūṭavanālayaḥ|
apātayadrathe tasya vindhye vajram ivāhihā|| 151.42||
sa rathastena śṛṅgeṇa nandinā dṛḍham āhataḥ|
sacakrakūbarahayaḥ pāṃsusāyujyam āgamat|| 151.43||
tato 'andhakarathaṃ dṛṣṭvā sacakrākṣaṃ vicūrṇitam|
nedurdevāḥ sagandharvāḥ pramathāśca saguhyakāḥ|| 151.44||
tato 'andhakastriśūlena naditvā kālameghavat|
nandinaṃ tāḍayāmāsa gajendra iva pādapam|| 151.45||
triśūlidayitastena triśūlenābhitāḍitaḥ|
nandī vihvalasarvāṅgaścakampe 'antarjalenduvat|| 151.46||
nandīśvare ghūrṇamāne prahāreṇa bhṛśārdite|
asurāṇāṃ bale jajñe simhanādaravo muhuḥ|| 151.47||
siṃhanādena śatrūṇāṃ tena nandī prabodhitaḥ|
paraśvadhenābhyahanadandhakaṃ bhūtabāndhavaḥ|| 151.48||
paraśvadhahato raktaṃ cakṣarāndhakadānavaḥ|
gajadantāhato raktaṃ svarasaṃ candano yathā|| 151.49||
andhakaṃ virathaṃ dṛṣṭvā rarakṣuramaradviṣaḥ|
āśāsvavasthitā devāsyathā lokam imaṃ tathā|| 151.50||
atha bāṇo baleḥ putro bāṇapuṣpasamaprabhaḥ|
andhakaṃ rathayānena sampādayata dānavaḥ|| 151.51||
sa taṃ rathaṃ dānavendra āruroha tadāndhakaḥ|
yathodayaṃ tu bhagavān dinakṛt pūrṇamaṇḍalaḥ|| 151.52||
tataḥ punaryujyata devadānavaiḥ prakartukāmaiḥ kalahaṃ sudāruṇam|
triśūlavajrāśanisāyakai raṇe pradhūpito 'agnirjvalitastarāṃ babhau|| 151.53||
|| iti skandapurāṇe
andhakanandiyuddha ekapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 151.151||

dvipañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
viṣṇum ardayamānaṃ tu dānavān dānavārdanam|
jambho 'ambuda ivārāvaṃ kṛtvā dudrāva dānavaḥ|| 152.1||
tam āpatantaṃ dṛṣṭvā tu jambham ambudanisvanam|
na sa saṃvivije devaḥ siṃho dṛṣṭveva kuñjaram|| 152.2||
kujambhaścaiva jambhaśca yavīyān dānavācalaḥ|
anantam antaṃ śatrūṇām āvavāra rarāsa ca|| 152.3||
vṛtro 'añjanagiriprakhyaḥ saṃvarttakanikāśadṛk|
jighṛkṣurabhyagādidraṃ nadamānaḥ payodavat|| 152.4||
taṃ dhāvantaṃ nadantaṃ ca dānavaṃ śatalocanaḥ|
kuhare girīsaṃkāśam ājaghāna purandaraḥ|| 152.5||
bhāvayatyo gadāyodhī śatāyuṃ vāyum āhave|
yoddhukāmo 'abhyayāt tūrṇaṃ jagarja ca jahāsa ca|| 152.6||
tuhuṇḍahuṇḍāvaśvibhyām ayudhyetāṃ mahāsurau|
prahlādena bhagaḥ sārdham aṃśena ca virocanaḥ|| 152.7||
aryamāṇaṃ yamaṃ caivāyudhyetāṃ bilvakelvalau|
vipracittimukhā ye ca baliṣvagrā mahāsurāḥ|| 152.8||
gaṇeśvarāṃste devāṃśca ayudhyanta sahasraśaḥ|
andhakastu samāgamya nandinaṃ dānavarṣabhaḥ|| 152.9||
tatakṣe vatsaradanaiḥ śaraiḥ kārmukaniḥsṛtaiḥ|
so 'andhakena dṛḍhaṃ viddhaḥ śarairmarmavidāraṇaiḥ|| 152.10||
cukopa nandī kruddhaśca sasārāndhakam āhave|
savajram udyamya karaṃ divākarakaraprabham|| 152.11||
rarāsa nandī saṃrabdhaḥ payoda iva saṃkṣaye|
vajreṇa śatadhāreṇa so 'andhakasya gaṇeśvaraḥ|| 152.12||
cūrṇayāmāsa turagān niyantāraṃ rathaṃ tathā|
tato 'andhakaṃ karṇamūle kuṇḍalālakaśobhite|| 152.13||
ājaghāna ghanārāvo varadaścārukuṇḍalaḥ|
tenāpyapāvṛtya hasto hastihastanibhastataḥ|| 152.14||
pātito nandinaḥ kroḍe kuñjareṇeva saṃyuge|
apahastāhatastena dānavena gaṇeśvaraḥ|| 152.15||
apāsarpat padānyaṣṭau tānyevāpatitaḥ punaḥ|
sādhu sādhviti vai daityāstato hyandhakam abruvan|| 152.16||
sa tena suprahāreṇa dānavaṃ prati roṣitaḥ|
krodham āhārayaṃstīvram abhidudrāva caiva hi|| 152.17||
tasya gatvā dhanuścitraṃ kavacaṃ ca mahāprabham|
vajreṇa śatadhāreṇa khaṇḍaśaḥ pracakāra ha|| 152.18||
bāhupāśena caivainaṃ baddhvā bhūtapatiḥ svayam|
iyeṣa bhūmau niṣpeṣṭum andhakaścāvamocayat|| 152.19||
sa mocayitvā hi ātmānaṃ māyām āsthāya mohanīm|
abhidudrāva śailādiṃ tiṣṭha tiṣṭheti cocivān|| 152.20||
tam āpatantaṃ vegena gaṇeśvaramahattarāḥ|
sarve saṃkruddhamanaso vividhāyudhapāṇayaḥ|| 152.21||
nandiṣeṇaḥ somanandī śaṅkukarṇo mahodaraḥ|
ghaṇṭākarṇo vīrabhadraḥ sa ca devaḥ prabhāmayaḥ|| 152.22||
bhartāram abhirakṣantasteṣāṃ pāriṣadāgragāḥ|
andhakaṃ yodhayanti sma siṃhāḥ śakragajaṃ yathā|| 152.23||
taṃ nandiṣeṇaḥ śūlena somanandī ca muṣṭinā|
śareṇa vīrabhadraśca ghaṇṭākarṇo 'asināpi ca|| 152.24||
śaṅkukarṇaścalāgreṇa pādapena prabhāmayaḥ|
andhakaṃ cicchidurdevā dramiḍā iva candanam|| 152.25||
nandīśvarastu gaṇapo gaṇapairvimukhīkṛtam|
ājaghānottamāṅge tu andhakaṃ dānavādhipam|| 152.26||
dṛṣṭvāsurapatiṃ devairgaṇapaiḥ samabhidrutam|
asurāṇāṃ bale jajñe dhāva gṛhṇeti nisvanaḥ|| 152.27||
tato 'asurāḥ samājagmuḥ prahlādapramukhā drutam|
tān yuddhāyāgatāneko viṣṇuḥ sarvānadīdharat|| 152.28||
cakrahastaṃ tu dṛṣṭvaivaṃ vikrāntaṃ raṇamūrdhani|
cakāra sumahadvegam andhakaḥ krodhamūrchitaḥ|| 152.29||
vyāyacchamānaṃ niśceṣṭaṃ pradhāvantaṃ pragarjitam|
yaṃ yataḥ paśyate 'asau vai taṃ taṃ vivyādha sāyakaiḥ|| 152.30||
pṛthavaḥ pītaniśitā garuḍāṅgaruhandharāḥ|
andhakasya śarā ghorāścyavante dhanuṣo 'akṣayāḥ|| 152.31||
mukheṣu dantaveṣṭeṣu udareṣu kareṣu ca|
andhakena gajā viddhāstyajantyatimadā madam|| 152.32||
anye :srayanti deveśam anye cendraṃ surādhipam|
devaṃ nārāyaṇaṃ cānye nandinaṃ cāpare gaṇāḥ|| 152.33||
anye śākhaṃ viśākhaṃ ca kumāram api cāpare|
vyapāśritya sthitā devāḥ śakuntā iva pādapān|| 152.34||
yathāśanibhayānmartyā yathā siṃhabhayānmṛgāḥ|
yathā ca garuḍānnityaṃ bhujagā bhujagāśinaḥ|| 152.35||
tathāndhakasya yuddhasthā devā daivatavairiṇaḥ|
vitresuḥ surajālārttā mūḍhā iva ca babhramuḥ|| 152.36||
bandhujīvavanaṃ yadvadbhrājate puṣpasannatam|
tathā vraṇajasiktāṅgaṃ tadbabhau pārṣadaṃ balam|| 152.37||
kampante pādapā yadvat kānaneṣvanileritāḥ|
tathāndhakabhayāddevāḥ santrastā raṇamūrdhani|| 152.38||
tato nārāyaṇo 'ananta ūrjitaḥ śakra eva ca|
aśvinau vasavaścāṣṭau ādityā dvādaśaiva ca|| 152.39||
nandī viśākhaḥ śākhaśca vīrabhadraḥ prabhāmayaḥ|
viṭpatiḥ śaṅkukarṇaśca somanandī vināyakaḥ|| 152.40||
ete bale hanyamāne andhakena balormibhiḥ|
dudruvuḥ sāyudhā devāstaṃ dānavagaṇādhipam|| 152.41||
gandharvabhavanākāraṃ taṃ tasya rathasattamam|
parivārya babhañjuste jagarjuśca payodavat|| 152.42||
bhajyamānaḥ surairāsīdandhakasya mahārathaḥ|
adharme prakṛto yadvadvighnairiva manorathaḥ|| 152.43||
cakrāyudhaṃ sa cakreṇa śakraṃ vajreṇa dānavaḥ|
anantam iṣuṇaikena śūlena ca vināyakam|| 152.44||
muṣṭinā nandinaṃ caiva paṭṭiśena prabhāmayam|
bhallena caiva pūṣāṇaṃ gadayā yamam eva ca|| 152.45||
āhatya vairiṇastūrṇaṃ sarvāneva raṇe 'andhakaḥ|
utpatya cānadadvyomni jalamatta ivāmbudaḥ|| 152.46||
sa kūṭayodhī kūṭāni girīṇāṃ girisannibhaḥ|
savṛkṣakṣupasarpāṇi sasarja ca jagarja ca|| 152.47||
giryagravarṣaṃ tadghoraṃ savṛkṣarkṣamahoragam|
papāta devasainyeṣu śītam amburuheṣviva|| 152.48||
avirāmam aviśrāmaṃ nirucchvāsaṃ bhayākulam|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 152.49||
chinnanāsākṣidantauṣṭhā bhagnapādakaṭīkarāḥ|
uttrastodbhrāntacakitā dṛśyante pramathāmarāḥ|| 152.50||
saudhāgraśṛṅgopalaśastravarṣī muhuḥ sṛjan bhātyasuro 'ambarasthaḥ|
tā me-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 152.51||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- śabdam|
abjaṃ mahaddhūmalatāvṛtaṃ ca khadyotatulyaṃ ca mahāgnicūrṇam|| 152.52||
so 'apyāyitodvṛttasamudranādo nabhogato daivatasaṃghavairī|
muhuḥ sṛjatyeva mahāmbuvarṣaṃ yathāntakāle 'ambumugugravarṣam|| 152.53||
|| iti skandapurāṇe
andhakayuddha dvipañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 152.152||

tripañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato 'andhako viyatsthito mahāmbudaughasannibhaḥ|
visṛjya varṣam aupalaṃ yathaiva varṣam ambudaḥ|| 153.1||
punaḥ pragṛhya kārmukaṃ mahendrakārmukopamam|
mumoca bāṇadurdinaṃ babhūva cātidurdinam|| 153.2||
tataḥ suparṇapuṅkhināṃ suparṇapatrapatriṇām|
suparṇatulyapātināṃ suparṇatuṅgatuṇḍinām|| 153.3||
śataṃ śarīrabhedināṃ śarīrasārabhojinām|
sasarja dānavādhipo jagarja cāpi darpitaḥ|| 153.4||
dhanuḥ prapūriteritā raṇapracāritairvṛtāḥ|
svamārgayānadeśikā jave manonilopamāḥ|| 153.5||
maheṣavo 'andhakasya te patanti devatopari|
yathā divākareritāḥ karā mahācaleṣviva|| 153.6||
śarāhatāśca kuñjarāḥ śarāhatāśca vājinaḥ|
śarāhatāśca devatā gaṇeśvarāśca sarvataḥ|| 153.7||
vinirgatāntraśoṇitā vikīrṇahārabhūṣaṇāḥ|
vimuktakeśabandhanāḥ patanti gāḍhavedanāḥ|| 153.8||
sthitaṃ calantam utthitaṃ pradhāvitaṃ pravalgitam|
hayaṃ gajaṃ suraṃ yathā prapaśyate hi yaṃ yataḥ|| 153.9||
tam andhakastadā ripuṃ śaraistamorivigrahaiḥ|
balānnipatya nardate jalāgame yathāmbudaḥ|| 153.10||
vraṇārttamuktanisvanaṃ samudbhramatturaṅgamam|
balaṃ nadīnavadbabhau praśāntatūryanisvanam|| 153.11||
vibhinnacchinnadāritaṃ pradagdhajagdhanirdhutam|
yathā madāndhakuñjarapraṇaṣṭapādapaṃ vanam|| 153.12||
mukheṣu kecidāhatā nirīkṣaṇeṣu cāpare|
urodareṣu cāpare tathā hatāśca pṛṣṭhataḥ|| 153.13||
śataghnayo yathācitāḥ śaraistathā marudgaṇāḥ|
gaṇāśca bhīmavikramā na bhūmim āpurāhatāḥ|| 153.14||
surāsuraiḥ pravartitā tato vraṇāmbuvāhinī|
gajendranakrasaṃkulā rathāṅgacārukacchapā|| 153.15||
nikṛttahastapannagā dhanurdhvajottamadrumā|
kirīṭakūṭadardurā dhanurguṇābhitantukā|| 153.16||
vikīrṇahāraśarkarā sitāmbarātipheninī|
surāsuraiḥ pravartitā surāsurātudistarā|| 153.17||
tato 'añjanāmudatviṣastaḍitprahāsahāsinaḥ|
piśācayakṣarākṣasāḥ pipāsayātikarṣitāḥ|| 153.18||
surā yathā varāmṛtaṃ papustathaiva śoṇitam|
tataḥ punaḥ samākulaṃ babhūva yuddham adbhutam|
tadāndhake śarāhate maheṣuṇātha nandine|| 153.19||
|| iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhabhūmivarṇana tripañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 153.153||

catuṣpañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
hanyamāne bale tasmin devaiḥ sapramatheśvaraiḥ|
cukrudhurdānavā ghorāścaturviṃśatidarpitāḥ|| 154.1||
prahlādaścānuhlādaśca saṃhlādaḥ śitivāṣkulau|
jambho virocano vṛtro balirbāṇo 'avaniṃjayaḥ|| 154.2||
tathā tuhuṇḍo huṇḍaśca śambhuḥ kārtasvanaḥ kubhaḥ|
śambaro vipracittiśca ilvakaḥ pilvakastathā|| 154.3||
mayastārastārak.ākṣo vidyunmālī pramohanaḥ|
ete 'amarṣavaśaṃ prāptāścaturviṃśatidānavāḥ|| 154.4||
dudruvuḥ sāyudhaṃ devaṃ nandinaṃ samavasthitam|
te 'añjanācalasaṃkāśāḥ kāñcanācalasannibham|| 154.5||
nandinaṃ tāḍayāmāsuḥ śūlaśaktyṛṣṭipaṭṭiśaiḥ|
tathā tairaribhiḥ "astraistāḍito vāritaśca vai|| 154.6||
nākṣubhyata tadā nandī nārttim āpanna ca vyathām|
tato vikṛṣya bhagavān ātataṃ kārmukaṃ mahat|| 154.7||
tribhistribhirbibhedāśu sarvān dānavasattamān|
te bāṇamārganisrāvairdānavāḥ śoṇitakṣarāḥ|| 154.8||
kṣaranta iva śailendrāstapanīyarasān babhuḥ|
tatastoṣoddhato nandī śukreṇojjīvitaṃ punaḥ|| 154.9||
kārttasvanaṃ śarairghorairanayadyamasādanam|
jīvitasraṃsanaṃ prāpya sa dānavamahācalaḥ|| 154.10||
śīrṇopalaḥ papātāśu vajrāhata ivācalaḥ|
patamāne kṣitau tasmin nandibāṇāhate hate|| 154.11||
balirutpāṭya śailāgraṃ cikṣepoddiśya nandinaṃ |
tat sadhātumṛgavyālaṃ sarkṣavṛkṣaṃ girestaṭam|| 154.12||
nirbhrāntopalavṛkṣālam abhyadhāvadgaṇeśvaram|
śṛṅgasya balimuktasya tasya vyālādayo javāt|| 154.13||
apakrāntānayārttasya puruṣasyeva bāndhavāḥ|
tadāpatat tadgiryagraṃ nandī bāṇena vīryavān|
meghāniva mahāvāyurbibheda ca nanāda ca|| 154.14||
tadvidārya gireḥ śṛṅgaṃ giriśṛṅganiketanaḥ|
baliṃ bibheda bāṇena balirvighnam ivotthitam|| 154.15||
so 'abhyāhato gaṇeśena prāhlāditanayo vaśaḥ|
papāta sahasā bhūmau vātāhata iva drumaḥ|| 154.16||
tato balau nipatite nandīṣuvaratāḍite|
jahuḥ sasamaramārāt taṃ dānavāḥ śarapīḍitāḥ|| 154.17||
prasṛtāmbudasaṃkāśāṃstato 'ambudanibhākṛtiḥ|
andhakaḥ khāt kṣitin prāpya dānavānidam abravīt|| 154.18||
adya dākṣāyaṇīputrā nibodhadhvaṃ vaco mama|
mayā coktāni pathyāni kurudhvaṃ yadi mayanta|| 154.19||
kuleṣu jātā vīrāśca sarvāstrakṛtaniścayāḥ|
dravadhve vai kim uddiśya paṭunārācavejitāḥ|| 154.20||
jalpitāni kva vastāni kathitāni ca saṃsadi|
kva vastadvairabāhulyaṃ daivataiḥ saha sāmpratam|| 154.21||
ekena nandinā bhagnāḥ śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|
hrīḥ kathaṃ vai na bhavati jalpatāṃ vo gṛhājire|| 154.22||
nivartadhvam adharmajñā yudhyadhvaṃ kiṃ sṛtena vai|
bhavenna no yatra mṛtyuḥ so 'avakāśo na vidyate|| 154.23||
prāśnikāḥ pārśvataḥ sthitvā nirvairā vītamatsarāḥ|
dvairathaṃ nandinā sārdham etat paśyata sāmpratam|| 154.24||
ityandhakavacaḥ śrutvā sarve te dānavā raṇe|
punarnivṛttā yuddhāya pragṛhītavarāyudhāḥ|| 154.25||
tato 'anyaṃ ratham āsthāya nalvamātraṃ patākinam|
andhakaḥ so 'abhyayānnandiṃ sārdhaṃ dānavapuṅgavaiḥ|| 154.26||
śitāgrarukmavikṛtāḥ pṛthavaḥ priyadarśanāḥ|
andhakasya dhanuḥsṛṣṭā niṣpatanti maheṣavaḥ|| 154.27||
śalabhairiva kedārā bhramarairiva pādapāḥ|
toyadairiva nāgendrāḥ sāgarā makarairiva|| 154.28||
maheṣubhirvinirmuktairnāgādityasamaprabhaiḥ|
andhakena kṛtā devāḥ śataghnaya ivottamāḥ|| 154.29||
vāyavo 'apratighā yadvadyathā mṛtyuryathā jarā|
yathā cāpratighāḥ sūktā niyataṃ brāhmaṇāśiṣaḥ|| 154.30||
tathā te niśitā hyugrā brahmadaṇḍā ivodyatāḥ|
anivāryā hyamoghāśca te 'andhakasya maheṣavaḥ|| 154.31||
yato yato 'asurāḥ sarve so 'andhakaśca raṇe ripuḥ|
tatastataḥ sma dīryante pramathā vibudhaiḥ saha|| 154.32||
so 'api nityāyatadhanuḥ pariveṣīva bhāskaraḥ|
asṛjadbāṇanikarān kiraṇān bhāskaro yathā|| 154.33||
tasya bāṇarujaḥ prāpya nadītīra iva drumāḥ|
sīdanti gaṇapāḥ sarve devāśca sahavāsavāḥ|| 154.34||
sa viṣṇum ekena śareṇa viddhvā dvābhyām anantaṃ tribhireva śakram|
yamaṃ ca somaṃ ca jalādhipaṃ ca vasūṃśca nirdārya rarāsa ghoram|| 154.35||
aśvidvayaṃ cāpi śaradvayena viddhvā bhagāṃśāryamacandrapūṣṇaḥ (?)|
tato 'atha nandīśvaram ugrakarmā gaṇeśvarāṃścāpi śaraistatakṣa|| 154.36||
tathā dahatyandhaka ātatāyī yathā pataṅgān bhagavān hutāśaḥ|
nivāritāste śaradāritāśca tadāndhakenāmarayodhamukhyāḥ|| 154.37||
na spandituṃ śekurudīkṣituṃ vā raṇe 'andhakaṃ khe manujā ivārkam|
yaśāṃsi dīptāni tataḥ prahāya devāḥ sanārāyaṇadevapālāḥ|
śarārditāste 'andhakadānavena pradudruvurdānavavedhakhinnāḥ|| 154.38||
viṣṇuḥ pitāmahaścaiva ananto 'atha śatakratuḥ|
andhakena raṇe bhagnāḥ śarairagniśikhopamaiḥ|| 154.39||
ādityā vasavaḥ sādhyā aśvinau ca surottamau|
andhakena raṇe bhagnā vajrāghātaiḥ patattrivat|| 154.40||
tuṣitāścaiva viśvāśca devāścaiva svadhābhujaḥ|
andhakena śarairbhagnā mārutena yathā drumāḥ|| 154.41||
candramā bhagavān vahnirvittapālaśca rākṣasaḥ|
andhakena raṇe bhagnāḥ śarairāśīviṣopamaiḥ|| 154.42||
gandharvā guhyakāḥ sarpā garuḍāśca mahoragāḥ|
andhakena raṇe bhagnā viddhānalasamaiḥ śaraiḥ|| 154.43||
viṭpatiḥ śaṅkukarṇaśca somanandī prabhāmayaḥ|
piṅgalo nandiṣeṇaśca ghaṇṭākarṇo mahodaraḥ|| 154.44||
vidyutkeśaḥ sukeśaśca sa ca devo vināyakaḥ|
anye ca pramathāḥ śūrā vīrabhadrapurogamāḥ|| 154.45||
andhakena raṇe bhagnāḥ śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|
trailokyaṃ prasabhaṃ sarvam udyuktaṃ sacarācaram|| 154.46||
andhakena raṇe bhagnaḥ sanārāyaṇadevapam|
tasmin surabale devaṃ vimucyaikaṃ gaṇādhipam|| 154.47||
mahāmaṇiśiromauliṃ na ka kaścidavatasthitavān|
tato 'asurabale ghoraḥ sarvaprāṇikṛto mahān|
siṃhanādaravo jajñe savāditraravo 'adbhutaḥ|| 154.48||
|| iti skandapurāṇe 'andhakavijaye
catuṣpañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 154.154||

pañcapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
etasminnantare devāḥ sarve śakrapurogamāḥ|
brahmaṇā sahitā jagmuḥ śaraṇyaṃ śūlapāṇinam|| 155.1||
te praṇamya mahādevam idam ūcurbhayārditāḥ|
vijitāḥ sarva eva smaḥ kim andhakam upekṣase|| 155.2||
devadevastataḥ prāha devān brahmapurogamān|
mayā dattavaro yasmāt tasmādyūyaṃ vinirjitāḥ|| 155.3||
krīḍārtham eva ca mayā saṃgare sa upekṣitaḥ|
adhunā bhavatām arthe śāmayiṣye 'aham andhakam|| 155.4||
tato devaḥ smitaṃ kṛtvā pārśvasthaṃ śūlam aikṣata|
devābhiprāyatattvajñaḥ śūlo jajvāla tatkṣaṇāt|| 155.5||
abhisṛtya drutaṃ caivam andhakaṃ jitakāśinam|
yuddhe vikramya sahasā nirbibheda stanāntare|| 155.6||
tato 'andhakaṃ tadā bhittvā sa śūlastaṃ mahābalam|
dānavendraṃ mahākāyam āninyeśaṅkarāntikam|| 155.7||
tasya bhinnasya śūlena ye 'akṣaran raktabindavaḥ|
patitāḥ puruṣā bhūtvā te 'apyayudhyanta duḥsahāḥ|| 155.8||
tasyaiva tulyarūpāste tasya tulyaparākramāḥ|
nānāśastrapraharaṇāste 'apyayudhyan gaṇeśvaraiḥ|| 155.9||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --$o$dyatapāṇayaḥ|
jaghnuḥ kecidgaṇāneva dravataste mahābalāḥ|| 155.10||
na teṣāṃ yudhyamānānāṃ kaścit tasthau gaṇeśvaraḥ|
saṃgrāme dānavendrāṇāṃ bhayāt sarve pradudruvuḥ|| 155.11||
tān dṛṣṭvā vidrutān sarvān gaṇān saha sureśvaraiḥ|
mahādevo 'asṛjat -- --$F$ $E$-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 155.12||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --karantadā|
-- vā vijñāpatyāmāsurājñāṃ no dātum arhasi|| 155.13||
devadevastadā prāha sarvāsḥ praharaṇodyatāḥ|
asṛgbindusamudbhūtān bhakṣayadhvaṃ mahāsurān|| 155.14||
evam uktāstu tāḥ sarvā yogeśvaryo mahābalāḥ|
hatvā hatvāsurān yuddhe cakhāduśca ma -- -- --|| 155.15||
devo 'api jvalitaṃ śūlam abravīdandhakāntakṛt|
andhakaṃ paca sūryāgnau sahasraṃ śaradāṃ śatam|| 155.16||
andhako 'api hi śūlāgre pacyamāno 'arkatejasā|
pūrṇe sahasre varṣāṇāṃ sāttvikaṃ bhāvam abhyagāt|| 155.17||
sāttvikaṃ bhāvam āpanno vinirdhūtarajastamaḥ|
lokānāṃ kāraṇaṃ devaṃ bubudhe govṛṣadhvajam|| 155.18||
taṃ buddhvā ca tato bhaktyā nirmalenāntarātmanā|
snāyvasthiśeṣastuṣṭāva devaṃ candrārdhamaulinam|| 155.19||
andhaka uvāca|
kṛtsnasya yo 'asya jagataḥ sacarācarasya kartā kṛtasya ca tathā sukhaduḥkhadātā|
saṃhāraheturapi yaḥ punarantakāle taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.20||
yaṃ yogino vigatamohatamorajaskā bhaktyaikatānamanaso vinivṛttakāmāḥ|
dhyāyanti niścitadhiyāmitadivyabhāvaṃ taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.21||
yaścandrakhaṇḍam amalaṃ vikasanmayūkhaṃ baddhvāsayaṃ (?) priyatayā śirasā bibharti|
yaścārdhadeham adadadgirirājaputryai taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.22||
yaḥ siddhacāraṇaniṣevitacārutoyāṃ gaṅgāṃ mahormirabhasāṃ gaganāt patantīm|
mūrdhnā dadhe srajam ivāpratilolapuṣyāṃ taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.23||
kailāsaśṛṅgaśikharaṃ pravikampyamānaṃ kailāsaśṛṅgasadṛśena daśānanena|
yaḥ pādapadmaparipīḍanayā dadhāra taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.24||
yenāsakṛdditisutāśca danoḥ sutāśca vidyādharoragagaṇāśca varaiḥ samagrāḥ|
saṃyojitā munivarāḥ phalamūlabhakṣāstaṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.25||
dakṣādhvaraṃ ca nayanaṃ ca tathā bhagasya pūṣṇastadā daśanapaṅktim aśātayacca|
vyaṣṭambhayat kuliśayuktamahendrabāhuṃ taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.26||
-- kṛ -- -- trividhabandhavimokṣabhāvā jñānānvayaśrutagaṇairapi naiva yuktāḥ|
taṃ saṃśritāḥ sukhabhujaḥ puruṣā bhavanti taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.27||
agre 'amṛtasya ravikoṭisamānatejaḥ santrāsanaṃ vibudhasattamadānavānām|
yaḥ kālakūṭam apibat samudīrṇavegaṃ taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.28||
brahmendraviṣṇumarutāṃ ca saṣaṇmukhānāṃ yo 'adādvarān subahuśo bhagavān maheśaḥ|
nandiṃ ca mṛtyuvadanāt prabhurujjahāra taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.29||
kāmaśca kārmukadharo bhuvi pañcabāṇo hāsyāt kṛto bhagavatā sa tadā videhaḥ|
ekeṣuṇā tripuram eva purā jaghāna taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.30||
ārādhitaḥ sutapasā himavannikuñje dhūmavratena manasāpi parairagamye|
saṃjīvanīm adita yaḥ paramārthagamyastasmai namaḥ śivakarāy śivāya nityam|| 155.31||
nānāvidhairgajaviḍālasamānavaktrairdakṣādhvarapramathanairvalibhirgaṇendraiḥ|
yo 'abhyarcyate 'amaragaṇaiḥ sahalokapālaistaṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.32||
krīḍārtham eva bhagavān bhuvanāni sapta nānānadīvihagapādapamaṇḍitāni|
sabrahmakāni sasṛje sukṛte hitāni taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.33||
yasyākhilaṃ jagadidaṃ vaśavarti nityaṃ yo 'aṣṭābhireva tanubhirbhuvanāni bhuṅkte|
yaḥ kāraṇaṃ sumahatām api kāraṇānāṃ taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.34||
-- -- -- -- --ṃ -- -- -- -- --ṃ -- -- -- --ṃ āsaya māṃ kṣitidharendrasutānuyāta|
-- -- -- -- -- -- --ma vibhūṣaṇāṅgaṃ taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.35||
baddhvā -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- taṃ śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇadaṃ śaraṇaṃ vrajāmi|| 155.36||
