dakṣādhvaraḥ suravaraiḥ kṛtasarvarakṣo bhṛgvādibhirmunivarairupagītavedaḥ|
krodhodbhavena tava deva hataḥ salīlam ekena śūlavaracakrabhṛtā gaṇena|| 155.69||
liṅgasya yo hara hariḥ pra -- -- hyadhastādūrdhvantvahaṃ -- -- -- -- -- -- -- bruvāṇaḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- ravandatavādimadhye ko 'anyaḥ pravīṇa iha vakṣyati te 'alpabuddhiḥ|| 155.70||
śarvo 'asi sarvagatasarvaphalaprado 'asi yogo 'asi yogadhara yogavidāṃ varo 'asi|
mātā pitāsi jagataḥ prabhuravyayo 'asi śāntaḥ śivo 'asi paramo 'asi śivaṃ karosi|| 155.71||
stavam imam amalārthaṃ brahmaṇā gītam agryaṃ dvijasadasi paṭhedyaḥ kalyam utthāya śaśvat|
iha sukham anubhūya pretya cāgre ca tasya dhanakanakasamṛddhe jāyate janma vaṃśe|| 155.72||
iti skandapurāṇe pañcapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 155.155||

ṣaṭpañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ stutaḥ sa bhagavān brahmaṇāyugmalocanaḥ|
uvāca devāṃstān sarvān brahmaṇā sahitāṃstadā|| 156.1||
prīto 'asmi vibudhā yāta nāśito devakaṇṭakaḥ|
kim anyat karavāṇyadya priyaṃ vo varatānaghāḥ|| 156.2||
ityuktā devadevena devāḥ sarve babhāṣire|
stuvantaḥ prahvamūrdhāno deveśaṃ hṛṣṭamānasāḥ|| 156.3||
tvam eva deva sarveṣām asmākaṃ śaraṇaṃ param|
tvaṃ pitā sarvalokānāṃ tvayāyaṃ nāśito 'andhakaḥ|| 156.4||
ityuktvā vibudhāḥ sarve praṇipatya ca śaṅkaram|
brahmaṇā sahitā jagmuryathāsthānaṃ mudā yutāḥ|| 156.5||
tato gaṇānapīśāno yuddha -- -- kṛtaśramān|
arcayitvā yathāvaddhi visasarja mahāmanāḥ|| 156.6||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
evaṃ tam andhakaṃ jitvā kṛtvā ca gaṇanāyakam|
visṛjyaca surān devo vijahāra surārtihā|| 156.7||
imaṃ yo hyandhakavadhaṃ paṭheta dvijasaṃsadi|
brāhmaṇo labhate -- -- -- yo rakṣāṃ na saṃśayaḥ|| 156.8||
śarīra -- -- -- yogaṃ rūpaṃ dharmaṃ ca vindati|
yacchrutvā gāṇapatyena yujyate dehaparyaye|| 156.9||
iti skandapurāṇe ṣaṭpañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 156.156||

saptapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
anugṛhyāndhakaṃ devo visṛjya sagaṇān surān|
carācareśas yaccakre tanmamācakṣva tattvataḥ|| 157.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
divaṃ deveṣu yāteṣu gaṇape cāndhake kṛte|
deveśo 'andhakanandibhyāṃ saha devyā -- -- -- --|| 157.2||
cirasya candramaulistu pramathādhipatirgṛhān|
praviśya rañjayāmāsa -- -- ṃ merugṛhāniva|| 157.3||
somāṃ somānuvadanāṃ somārdhatilako haraḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
sakhīnāṃ dṛśyate madhye tārāṇām iva rohiṇī|| 157.4||
dṛṣṭvā devyapi deveśam upāyātaṃ vṛṣadhvajam|
uttasthau āsanāt tūrṇaṃ sakhībhiḥ sahitā tadā|| 157.5||
śirasyañjalim ādhāya padmakuḍmalasannibham|
vavande caraṇau tasya prīyamāṇena cetasā|| 157.6||
devo 'api tāṃ samutthāpya tayaiva sahitaḥ prabhuḥ|
niṣasādāsane ratnamayūkhaparipiñjare|| 157.7||
andhakaṃ ca jitaṃ yuddhe devyāḥ priyacikīrṣayā|
śaṅkaraḥ kathayāmāsa punaśca pravarīkṛtam|| 157.8||
andhako 'ayaṃ tava suto mamaiva nayanodbhavaḥ|
āsuraṃ tyājito bhāvaṃ tvām avajñātavān hi naḥ|| 157.9||
ityuktavati deveśe śaṃkare 'andhakadānavaḥ|
praṇataḥ prāñjalirbhūtvā vyajñāpayata pārvatīm|| 157.10||
devyandhako 'ahaṃ devena prakṛtānugrahaḥ śubhe|
tava preṣyatvam āyātaḥ paśya māṃ saumyacakṣuṣā|| 157.11||
amba tanme vyatikrāntaṃ yanme dānavajaṃ tava(?)|
devenānugṛhīto 'ahaṃ tava hāsaśca kiṃkaraḥ|| 157.12||
kṣāntaṃ dāntaṃ ca bhaktaṃ ca tvadāśrayaparāyaṇam|
viddhi mām amba śuddhena bhāvena samavasthitam|| 157.13||
ityevam uktvā girijāṃ girikūṭanibho 'andhakaḥ|
vāgbhirāhavanīyābhirastuvat prāñjalirnataḥ|| 157.14||
vibhāvarī vāricarī śarvarī śarvavallabhā|
dhṛtirmatistathā kīrtirdīptiḥ prāptiḥ pramohinī|| 157.15||
medhā sudhā tathā sādhvī svadhā svāhā mahādyutiḥ|
puṣṭiriṣṭistathā tuṣṭirgṛṣṭirdṛṣṭistruṭistaḍit|| 157.16||
smṛtiḥ prītiḥ spṛhā hānirvāṇī glānirdayā kriyā|
lakṣmīḥ śrīḥ sannatiḥ śraddhā māyā māyādharārcitā|| 157.17||
aditirditistathā kadrūḥ siṃhikā surasā danuḥ|
rākā kuhūḥ sinīvālī carṣaṇī sukhadāyinī|| 157.18||
dīkṣā dakṣāvarā rakṣā śikṣā kakṣaniketanā|
sugandhā subhagā bhavyā bhūtabhavyabhavatkarī|| 157.19||
dharaṇī dhāraṇī dhanyā vīraṇī vai guhāraṇī|
-- lā golā tathā caiva maṅgalāvidhā-- tathā|| 157.20||
-- rovṛtā satā -- śca -- -- sakṣatranandinī (?)|
nakṣatracitrā dyauḥ pṛthvi kriyā smṛtiralolupā|| 157.21||
śuddhā śuddhiḥ sudhīḥ kīrtiḥ kṛttivāso 'adharapriyā|
dhanurjyā jayinī pūjyā ījyā vrajyā jayapradā|| 157.22||
varā vareṇyā varadā varanārī vacoraṇiḥ|
bhūtirbhūtādhijananī sukṛtiḥ sumanā ratiḥ|| 157.23||
bhāratī bhāsam āyuktā yuktaraktavacodharī|
ājñā prajñā tathā saṃjñā ulkā nāsāsamudbhavā|
vedamātātha gāyatrī durgā sāvitryathāpi ca|| 157.24||
dharmiṇī dharmajananī tejanī tejasāṃ varā|
rajanī rañjanī dhīrā yonirvanajalocanā|| 157.25||
śradarthinī danunadī śrutārthā śrutavattarā|
balayālātakadharā mekhalā mekhalādharā|| 157.26||
prīyatāṃ me jagaddhartrī śyāmā śyāmāmbarā hyumā|
ityevam andhakeneśā stutā stutiśatastutā|| 157.27||
andhakasya tutoṣāti tuṣṭā cedam uvāca tam|
prītāsmi putra yat prāptaṃ gāṇapatyaṃ tvayā śubham|
priyo 'adhunā varastūrṇaṃ vriyatāṃ pravarottama|| 157.28||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
bhavānīṃ varadāṃ dṛṣṭvā so 'andhako gaṇapottamaḥ|
praṇataḥ prāñjaliḥ prāha himavattanayām umām|| 157.29||
yaṃ ca tvaṃ me varaṃ devi dadāsīśānavallabhe|
mama tena samastena tvayi bhaktiḥ sthirā bhavet|| 157.30||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā bhagavatyaparājitā|
uvācāndhakam āsādya prīyamāṇā punastadā|| 157.31||
jñānenānena tuṣṭā asmi tava putra śubhena vai|
yanmatto 'arthitavānadya tvaṃ bhaktiṃ pravareśvara|| 157.32||
macchandādeva cāpyetadgāṇapatyaṃ tavānagha|
dattaṃ devādhidevena tena cāsmi sutoṣitā|| 157.33||
tasmāccādityapākāt te suyuddhena ca putraka|
pāpavyayo mahān āsīt tenāsi pravarīkṛtaḥ|| 157.34||
amaro jarayā tyakto balī balavatām api|
tapasvī hyakṣayo jetā nandivat tvaṃ bhaviṣyasi|| 157.35||
mama devasya cāpīṣṭaḥ kiṃkaro mama cāpyatha|
bhava tvam anaghaḥ śrīmān gaṇeśvaragaṇeśvaraḥ|| 157.36||
ye ca tvāṃ kīrtayiṣyanti divā rātrāvathāpi vā|
teṣāṃ kīrtiryaśaḥ svargo dharmaścaiva bhaviṣyati|| 157.37||
sa tvevam uktaḥ pārvatyā andhako 'arcitamānitaḥ|
anujñātaśca pārvatyā mumude harapārśvagaḥ|| 157.38||
ityevam andhakaṃ devastamorikṛtamūṣaṇaḥ|
anugṛhya girau tasmin vijahāra yathāsukham|| 157.39||
|| iti skandapurāṇe andhakavarapradānaṃ nāma
saptapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 157.157||

aṣṭapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
anndhakaṃ gaṇapaṃ kṛtvā devyā saha maheśvaraḥ|
kiṃ cakre 'ataḥ paraṃ brūhi nuda kautūhalaṃ mama|| 158.1||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
jitvāndhakaṃ tato vyāsa kṛtvā ca gaṇanāyakam|
girīndrasutayā sārdhaṃ vijahāra surārttihā|| 158.2||
atha bhūteśajananī ṣaḍānanatanūkarī|
apṛcchat putrasambaddhaṃ praśnaṃ praśnavidāṃ varā|| 158.3||
kimarthaṃ gīyate deva gātheyaṃ sadbhiruttamā|
varaṃ bhūmiruhāḥ pañca na ca koṣṭharuhā daśa|| 158.4||
ṣoḍaśehāṅgam aṅgāni bhittvā putro 'abhijāyate|
tasmāt putrāt kathaṃ śreṣṭhaḥ koṣṭhajādbhuvijaḥ sutaḥ|| 158.5||
ityevaṃ pṛcchatīṃ pṛcchāṃ śikṣāṃ dīṣāṃ kriyāṃ matim|
umām anupamāṃ deva idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 158.6||
sūkṣmārtha eṣa rambhoru yaṃ pṛcchasi varānane|
ahaṃ te taṃ pravakṣyāmi śailendratanaye 'avyaye|| 158.7||
koṣṭhajāt tanayādyasmādbhūmijastanayo varaḥ|
śālmalau vaitaraṇyāṃ ca asipatravaneṣu|| 158.8||
kumbhīpāke raurave ca mahāraurava eva ca|
evamādyeṣu cānyeṣu kukṛtairanuveṣṭitān|
śāsyato mṛtyuvacanādrākṣasaiḥ krūrakarmabhiḥ|| 158.9||
pitR̥ṃstathāśubhairghorairveṣṭitān rākṣasārditān|
satputrastrāyate devi netaraḥ pāpaniścayaḥ|| 158.10||
narasya na ca satputrāḥ sarva eva bhavantyuta|
eka evātra bhavati yaḥ pitR̥ṃstrāyate bhayāt|| 158.11||
tatra ye duṣṭacāritrāḥ putrasaṃkhyāṃ na te gatāḥ|
śaṭho yadvadbalīvardaḥ ṣaṇḍho vāpi narādhipaḥ|| 158.12||
tatrāpi codyate duḥkhaṃ duḥkhaṃ ca narakaṃ viduḥ|
yat pitR̥ṃstrāyate tasmāt sutaḥ putrastataḥ smṛtaḥ|| 158.13||
nānyaḥ sambaddhako devi pituḥ putrasya cobhayaḥ|
pāti putraṃ pitā tasmāt putro yat trāyate bhayāt|| 158.14||
indriyāṇāṃ tu prābalyāt tat putreṣvapi pārvati|
pāpakānyapi kurvanti te 'asatputrā bhavantyuta|| 158.15||
ime hi taravo devi dakṣaśāpāddhatendriyāḥ|
pāpakāni na kurvanti saṃvṛtaiḥ karaṇaiśca ha|| 158.16||
etasmāt kāraṇāddevi koṣṭhajānāṃ śatādapi|
eko bhūmiruhaḥ putraḥ śasyate na tu koṣṭhajaḥ|| 158.17||
chedaṃ bhedaṃ tathā trāsaṃ pāṭanācca niśācaraiḥ|
kurvadbhistaravaḥ putrāḥ pitR̥ṇāṃ -- -- -- $E$-- --|| 158.18||
umovāca|
chedaṃ bhedaṃ trāsanaṃ ca rākṣasairnirayopagaiḥ|
kathaṃ pitR̥ṇāṃ taravo vārayanti yamakṣaye|| 158.19||
devadeva uvāca|
śṛṇuṣva chedaṃ bhedaṃ ca pitR̥ṇāṃ yamasādane|
yathā vai pārayantyete taravo nāganandini|| 158.20||
ete nirudyamā devi vihīnāḥ karaṇairuta|
yajñe 'arthitāste devānāṃ taravo -- -- -- -- --|| 158.21||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
dakṣaśāpena bhagavan vayaṃ hyupahatendriyāḥ|| 158.22||
tamobāhulyatāṃ prāptā niṣkriyā niṣparikramāḥ|
asukhāḥ karaṇairhīnā mahatā tamasāvṛtāḥ|| 158.23||
etāṃ daśām anuprāptā dharmayuktān kuruṣva naḥ|
ityeṣāṃ vacanaṃ śrutvā devaḥ salilasambhavaḥ|| 158.24||
yajñavṛkṣārtham āhedaṃ vṛkṣān vṛkṣapatirvacaḥ|
sthāvarāḥ svāgataṃ vo 'astu tuṣyāmi śaraṇaiṣiṇām|
nāśayāmyeṣa vo vatsā dakṣaśāpakṛtaṃ tamaḥ|| 158.25||
śālā bilvāḥ palāśāśca varuṇāḥ kiṃśukāstathā|
rohītakāśca ye cānye yajñāṅgaprabhavā drumāḥ|| 158.26||
te sūpayuktā yajñeṣu tvakpatraphalaśākhinaḥ|
mūrtīḥ subhāsvarāḥ prāpya mama loke nivatsyatha|| 158.27||
eṣāṃ yajñiyavṛkṣāṇāṃ yūyam apyanugāminaḥ|
yajñopayuktā gacchadhvaṃ teṣām eva salokatām|| 158.28||
sthāṇuliṅgopayuktāśca janairbhaktipuraḥsaraiḥ|
dharmeṇa śuddhadehāśca gatim iṣṭām avāpsyatha|| 158.29||
upayogaṃ ca gacchanto yajñāyatanavastuṣu|
dakṣaśāpatamomuktā mama loke cariṣyatha|| 158.30||
putrahīno naro yaśca putrakān vaḥ kariṣyati|
taṃ bhayāt trāyatāṃ caiva dharmo vo bhavitā mahān|| 158.31||
tarava ūcuḥ|
kathaṃ vayaṃ putrakṛtāstān pitR̥n nirayopagān|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 158.32||
somavikrayiṇo ye ca ye ca viśvastaghātinaḥ|
ye ca prāṇivadhe yuktāḥ pṛṣṭhamāṃsāśinaśca ye|| 158.33||
rājñām ākrośakā ye ca ye ca piṇḍāpahārakāḥ|
ete svakarmabhirghorairveṣṭitā lomaharṣaṇaiḥ|| 158.34||
pacyante niraye ghore krośanto bhairavān ravān|
aho bhṛśaṃ yātanābhiraśivābhirabhidrutāḥ|| 158.35||
śāsyante mṛtyuvacanādrākṣasairbhīmavikramaiḥ|
tānevaṃ tudyamānāṃśca kuṭyamānāṃśca rākṣasaiḥ|
pitR̥n nirayasaṃmagnānuddhariṣyāmahe katham|| 158.36||
brahmovāca|
tāṃstathā tudyamānāṃśca kuṭyamānāṃśca rākṣasaiḥ|
pitR̥n nirayasaṃmagnān yūyam abhyuddhariṣyatha|| 158.37||
nirayasthān yathā caitān pitR̥n nistārayiṣyatha|
tanme sumanaso bhūtvā niśāmayata pādapāḥ|| 158.38||
putraprakṛtakā yūyaṃ yasya yasya bhaviṣyatha|
tasya tasya smṛtāḥ śīghraṃ taṃ deśaṃ yāsyathānaghāḥ|| 158.39||
-- -- -- nirayaprāptān pitR̥n kleśairupadrutān|
sukhāya dhāsyatha yathā sthāvarāstannibodhata|| 158.40||
mantravadvidhitaścaiva yo vaḥ saṃskāram antaśaḥ|
garbhādhānādibhiḥ kṛtvā putratve kalpayennaraḥ|| 158.41||
ye cāpi pūrvajātān yo vidhinā niṣparigrahān|
putraprakṛtakān kuryustāṃśca nistārayiṣyatha|| 158.42||
sarvakāmāṃśca dāsyadhvaṃ sukhaṃ caiva tathottamam|
karmakṣayaṃ ca sarveṣāṃ lokāṃścaiva tathākṣayān|| 158.43||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tataḥ śailasutā bhūyo 'apṛcchat tadvidhim uttamam|
tāṃ pṛcchatīṃ mahādeva idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 158.44||
devi nāgendranāsoru nāgendragatigāmini|
śṛṇuṣva yena vidhinā gṛhyate 'avanijaḥ sutaḥ|| 158.45||
śvo bhūte 'ahaṃ bhuviruhaṃ grahīṣyāmīti pārvati|
sopavāsā bhavennārī śuciśīlā ścivratā|| 158.46||
tataḥ śatasahasrāṃśāvastaśṛṅgaṃ gate ravau|
udite vimale cāpi candre candranibhānane|| 158.47||
āpadbhāvena subhage pareṇa paramātmike|
viprān āmantrayedrātrau pāvanān vedavādinaḥ|| 158.48||
śrutīnām ākarā hyete ratnānām iva sāgarāḥ|
viprā viprādhipamukhi pūjanīyāḥ sahasraśaḥ|| 158.49||
yatra mantravido viprā na prāśnantyuttamaṃ haviḥ|
na tatra devā deveśe havirbhuñjanti karhicit|| 158.50||
na skandate na vyathate nainam ākramate tamaḥ|
variṣṭham etaddānānāṃ yadbrāhmaṇamukhe hatam|| 158.51||
brahmaṇatve (?) mahāsattve aṇadhātustu bhakṣaṇe|
brahma bhakṣayate yasmādbrāhmaṇastena sa smṛtaḥ|| 158.52||
jāyante ye punarjātā hyupanītā mahātmabhiḥ|
tato devi dvijākhyeyaṃ teṣu nityaṃ nipātyatre|| 158.53||
viyadityucyate vyoma prakāraḥ prāpaṇe smṛtaḥ|
divaṃ samprāpayantyete devi viprāstataḥ smṛtāḥ|| 158.54||
satyasāramayā hyete viprāḥ sṛṣṭāḥ svayambhuvā|
siddhirna teṣvatuṣṭeṣu śakyāḥ prāptuṃ surairapi|| 158.55||
ahaṃ nārāyaṇo 'ananto brahmā śakro 'anilaḥ śikhī|
taddānaṃ nābhinandāmo viprā yatra na pūjitāḥ|| 158.56||
yeṣāṃ prasādāt sulabhā āyurdharmo balaṃ sukham|
śrīryaśaḥ svargavāsaśca tān viprānarcayedbudhaḥ|| 158.57||
viprān āmantrayitvātha śucivastrā śucismitā|
śayīta sanamaskārā sadarbhā bhūmim āśritā|| 158.58||
gamayitvā tato rātriṃ savitaryutthite 'api ca|
bhakṣyaṃ bhojyaṃ samādāya vrajedyatra bhavet taruḥ|| 158.59||
tatastaṃ sapatākaṃ ca sātapatraṃ sabhūṣaṇam|
tarukaṃ pramadā kṛtvā tarucchāyānugāminī|| 158.60||
yathopapannam annaṃ tu bhojayitvā dvijottamān|
puṇyāhaṃ kārayitvātha ṛtvijā hyathavātmanā|| 158.61||
tṛptānāṃ brāhmaṇānāṃ ca tattvenākūtam ātmanaḥ|
nivedya param uddiśya sadbhāvena pareṇa ha|| 158.61||
aputrā bhagavanto 'ahaṃ putraprakṛtakaṃ tarum|
grahīṣye tadanujñāṃ vai kartum arhatha me 'anaghāḥ|| 158.63||
tatastairabhyanujñātaṃ taṃ taruṃ taruṇaṃ priye|
bhūmidevasamakṣaṃ vai gṛhṇīyāt tanayaṃ priye|| 158.64||
anena vidhinā devi gṛhītastarukaḥ sutaḥ|
pitR̥ṇāṃ nirayasthānāṃ madhu so 'amuñca varṣati|| 158.65||
gṛhīto vidhinānena subhru bhūmiruhātmajaḥ|
śubhe sukhāya bhavati viparītena duḥkhadaḥ|| 158.66||
satputrāṇāṃ śatāccāpi devi candranibhānane|
eko bhūmiruhaḥ śreṣṭhaḥ putratve kalpitaḥ sutaḥ|| 158.67||
ityetat te mayā śiṣṭaṃ śriṣṭamliṣṭavacoraṇi|
yathā bhūmiruhaḥ putro viśiṣṭaḥ koṣṭhajāt sutāt|| 158.68||
tataḥ punardevadevī praṇipatya maheśvaram|
praṇayāt kautukāccaiva idaṃ vacanam abravīt|| 158.69||
proṣite tvayi deveśa bhramantyā mandare mayā|
aśokataruko dṛṣṭaḥ komalaḥ sumanoramaḥ|| 158.70||
asīcca me tadā bhāva eṣa me tarupotakaḥ|
bhaviṣyati suto rudre nirvighnaṃ punarāgate|| 158.71||
ābhyāṃ ca me mahādeva kucābhyāṃ dvijapāvana|
kṣīram āgāt sudhāsāraṃ putrasnehāt sukhapradam|| 158.72||
tam ahaṃ deva gṛhṇīyāṃ putraprakṛtakaṃ tarum|
yadi me kuruṣe 'anujñāṃ tavāhaṃ vaśavartinī|| 158.73||
devaiḥ putraphale kṣipte sa hi me tarupotakaḥ|
tuṣṭiprado hyaputrāyāḥ putrako bhavitānagha|| 158.74||
ityevaṃ bhāṣamāṇāṃ tu bhavānīṃ bhagavān bhavaḥ|
sadbhāvānniḥsṛtaṃ vākyam avadat paratāpanaḥ|| 158.75||
devi phullāravindākṣi kathaṃ nāma na te sutaḥ|
bhaviṣyasi tapasvinyā aiśvaryaparame mayā|| 158.76||
śaktā janayituṃ putrāṃstapasa tvam anindite|
ahaṃ ca te pradāsyāmi putrān paramaśobhanān|| 158.77||
athavāyam anugrāhyastavāśokataruḥ priye|
anujñātā mayā devi kurvaśokataruṃ sutam|| 158.78||
anukūlaṃ patiṃ jñātvā taṃ tāmarasalocanā|
praṇipatyāvyayā tuṣṭā idam āha maheśvaram|| 158.79||
deva jānāmyahaṃ dharmaṃ yathā strīṇāṃ na vidyate|
daivataṃ patim utsṛjya pūjanīyaṃ hi yadbhavet|| 158.80||
anāmantrya hi bhartāraṃ yaddadāti yadarcati|
na phalaṃ vindate tasya nārī ityeva naḥ śrutam|| 158.81||
yā tu bhartāram āmantrya nārī dharmaṃ samācaret|
tasyā devāśca tuṣyanti dharmaśca sumahān vibho|| 158.82||
avamanya tu yā nārī bhartāraṃ daivataṃ gurum|
svabuddhyā kurute puṇyaṃ nirayaṃ sā prapadyate|| 158.83||
atītam api yā nārī bhartāraṃ paripṛcchati|
anumānya yathāvaddhi jīvantam iva śobhanā|| 158.84||
anujñātā hi sā tena prīyamāṇena cetasā|
dharmakṛtyeṣu deveśa phalaṃ prāpnoti puṣkalam|| 158.85||
tapopavāso dānaṃ ca ārjavaṃ satyam eva ca|
patiśuśrūṣaṇasyaite kalāṃ nārghanti ṣoḍaśīm|| 158.86||
yā hyanyataralolāpi sadbhāvācchayanāsane|
śuśrūṣāṃ kurute bhartuḥ sā satyeva vibhāvyate|| 158.87||
ityevaṃ giritanayā girīśam uktvā giryagre giritarupuṣpapuñjacitre|
tenāgryā saha vicacāra cārurūpā bhānorbhā iva saha bhānunā bhavānī|| 158.88||
iti tau surapūjitāvaparasparapūjitau|
sahitau praviceratuḥ pravareśvaravanditau|| 158.89||
|| iti skandapurāṇe bhūmijaputravarṇane
aṣṭapañcāśaduttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 158.157||

ūnaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
pārvatyā niścayaṃ jñātvā bhagavāṃstryambakastadā|
sumāliṃ piṅgalaṃ yakṣaṃ prāha vākyavidāṃ varaḥ|| 159.1||
bhaktimantaṃ mahāyogaṃ purā labdhavaraṃ gaṇam|
pārśvasthaṃ nandinaṃ tatra bhagavāñchaṃkaraḥ svayam|| 159.2||
parvatendrasutāśokaṃ taruṃ putraṃ grahīṣyati|
tvayi āyattaṃ ca tat sarvaṃ tasmāt kuru mamājñayā|| 159.3||
yatrāśokatarustatra yathānnam upalakṣitam|
bhavet supracuraṃ vīra tathā kuru gaṇeśvara|| 159.4||
pradeśaśca girestasya yathā ramyo bhaviṣyati|
tathā vidhatsva yakṣendra yatrāśokataruḥ sthitaḥ|| 159.5||
ityuktaḥ parameśena piṅgalaḥ piṅgalekṣaṇaḥ|
uvāca somayā sārdhaṃ tridaśānāṃ patiṃ patim|| 159.6||
gaṇādhipa yathājñaptaṃ tat kariṣyāmi yajñahan|
yathā somaḥ sa nandī ca prasanno me bhaviṣyati|| 159.7||
ityuktvā so 'abhyanujñāto yakṣo lokānnadastadā|
tasyāśokataroḥ pārśve vidadhāvannam uttamam|| 159.8||
sumālāvatha niṣkrānte siṃhakrodhastrilocanaḥ|
nandinaṃ tejasāṃ rāśirdiṇḍicaṇḍeśvaro 'abravīt|| 159.9||
brahmaṇyān brahmaṇān nandin devī yajñena yakṣyati|
śvaḥ prabhāte mahābuddhe tatra vipraiḥ prayojanam|| 159.10||
sa tvaṃ matprahito deva yatra yatra vadāmyaham|
tatra tatra gato viprān nimantraya padatraye|| 159.11||
audakāyāṃ virūpāsya brāhmaṇā brahmasambhavāḥ|
upāsate ye varuṇaṃ pātālatalasaṃśrayāḥ|| 159.12||
ye surevyāsurādyāśca rasāvayavam uttamam|
pibanti phenapā nāma tān nimantraya mā ciram|| 159.13||
saṃyamanyāṃ tathā caiva ye yamaṃ paryupāsate|
brāhmaṇā brahmaṇā tulyāstān nimantraya bhūtapa|| 159.14||
tathodayagireḥ śṛṅge satyo nāma mahāhradaḥ|
rājahaṃsānucaritaḥ kāntatāmarasāvṛtaḥ|| 159.15||
vasanti yatra te satyāḥ satyānāma tapodhanāḥ
satyena yeṣām ādityo dinaṃ nayati nityaśaḥ|| 159.16||
teṣāṃ niṣkalmaṣastasmin hrade snāto divākaraḥ|
pratyahaṃ kurute devaḥ prayāṇaṃ śubhakarmakṛt|| 159.17||
teṣāṃ praṇamya śirasā hi ātmānaṃ sannivedya ca|
sadbhāvaṃ darśayannagre nandīśvara nimantraya|| 159.18||
ye cādityarathaṃ śaśvat parivārya vrajantyuta|
atharvāṅgirasastāṃśca nimantraya gaṇa dvijān|| 159.19||
ye ca cakracarāḥ siddhā ye kapotoñchavṛttayaḥ|
upāsate ye ca śakraṃ tān āmantraya vai dvijān|| 159.20||
tato brahmasado gatvā brahmaṇyān brahmaṇaḥ priyān|
brahmāṇaṃ ca sapatnīkaṃ brāhmaṇāṃśca nimantraya|| 159.21||
kṣīrodavelānilayāstapovananivāsinaḥ|
brahmaṇo bhavanādetya bālakhilyān nimantraya|| 159.22||
ye māṃ sadārāḥ sasutāḥ sāgnihotraparicchadāḥ|
bhaktā yeṣām ahaṃ nityaṃ prasādasumukho 'agraṇīḥ|| 159.23||
tān bālakhilyān vāgīśa vyālāniva durāsadān|
āmantraya yato bhūtvā suyaśāḥ suyaśāpate|| 159.24||
saṃcaraṃśca tribhuvanaṃ vāyuravyāhato yathā|
yān yataḥ paśyase viprān sarvāneva nimantraya|| 159.25||
ye cāpi pramathāḥ kecidgocare te surārihan|
te ca sarve samāyāntu viprāṇāṃ pariveśakāḥ|| 159.26||
kapardinaivam uktastu nandī sūryasamaprabhaḥ|
śūlaṃ jvalantam udyamya prayayau varuṇālayam|| 159.27||
sāgaraṃ so 'ambarākāraṃ sāmbaro 'ambagocaraḥ|
āsasāda pravalgantaṃ raṅgastham iva vāraṇam|| 159.28||
sa taṃ timiśatākīrṇam arṇavaṃ pramathāgraṇīḥ|
praviveśa pradīpto 'arkaḥ payodanicayaṃ yathā|| 159.29||
sutale sa tu pātāle gāṃ gajendrendravikramaḥ|
apaśyat kṣaratīṃ kṣīraṃ divyaṃ tadamṛtākaram|| 159.30||
surabhīm abhivādyaiva śaṃkarānucaro 'arihā|
viveśa nandī varuṇo yatrāste sagaṇo 'arcitaḥ|| 159.31||
sa divyavastrābharaṇaṃ putrapautragaṇānvitam|
apaśyadambugoptāram ādityāyutasannibham|| 159.32||
varuṇaṃ dvārapālena pūrvam eva niveditaḥ|
praviveśa tadā nandī varuṇasya niveśanam|| 159.33||
sa cāpyapāt tadā (?) rājā dūrādeva prahṛṣṭavat|
dṛṣṭvā nandinam uttasthau pūjayan manmathārdanam|| 159.34||
tasyārghaṃ gāṃ ca pādyaṃ ca nivedya varuṇaḥ svayam|
āsīnaṃ tam apāṃ goptā papraccha vadatāṃ varaḥ|| 159.35||
bhagavan kiṃ cirasyādya tvayā vayam apekṣitāḥ|
darśanaṃ devadevasya manyāmastava darśanāt|| 159.36||
vivaṣoriva te vaktram indragopāyate 'anagha|
vada sarvānabhiprāyān kartā te 'ahaṃ na saṃśayaḥ|| 159.37||
varuṇenaivam uktastu tatpareṇa śilādajaḥ|
tataḥ sa varuṇaṃ prāha dānavairaparājitam|| 159.38||
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ giriputrī grahīṣyati|
krīḍārtham umayā sārdhaṃ nimantrayati te haraḥ|| 159.39||
taddevaputrābhivṛtaḥ sadāraḥ saha phenapaiḥ|
śvo yāhi mandaragiriṃ prītiṃ vardhaya śūlinaḥ|| 159.40||
ityuktvā so 'abhyanujñāto varuṇena gaṇeśvaraḥ|
niṣkrānto varuṇāvāsācchvetābhrādiva bhāskaraḥ|| 159.41||
sa pūjyamānaḥ siddhaiśca cāraṇaiśca surairapi|
prāpodayagiriṃ nandī hareṣustripuraṃ yathā|| 159.42||
so 'atha tasya gireḥ śr.ṅge rañjite tāpanaiḥ karaiḥ|
nililye garuḍaḥ pakṣī prabhañjanapathe yathā|| 159.43||
hradaṃ tatrārṇavākāraṃ kāñcanāmbujaśobhitam|
śīrṇotpalataraṅgāḍhyam apaśyat so 'apsarovṛtam|| 159.44||
hradasya tasya rodhaḥsu sāśokeṣu sahasraśaḥ|
apaśyata ṛṣīn satyān ādityāyutasannibhān|| 159.45||
sa tāṃstapodhanān dṛṣṭvā tapanābhāṃstapodhanān|
nandī prahvāñjalipuṭo hi āsādyāvandata dvijān|| 159.46||
te sarve niyamān hitvā niyamasthāstapodhanāḥ|
nandinaṃ samayujyanta vāsadrumam ivāṇḍajāḥ|| 159.47||
taiḥ sūryakiraṇāpītaiḥ pītacīrāmbarairapi|
saṃvṛtaḥ sa babhau nandī jambudvīpa ivācalaiḥ|| 159.48||
sa pūjyamāno gaṇapaḥ satyaḥ satyaistapodhanaiḥ|
atīva prababhau vyāsa tīrtheṣviva maheśvaraḥ|| 159.49||
te nandinaṃ sukhāsīnaṃ satyaṃ satyāstapodhanāḥ|
ūcurharṣākulairvākyairvismitānanalocanāḥ|| 159.50||
nandīśvara cirasyādya hyudayo hyudayaprabhaḥ|
samākrāntastvayā tāta dharmeṇa nirayo yathā|| 159.51||
kim ihānagha deveśastrinetrastripurārdanaḥ|
vihartum āgato devo dṛṣṭo 'asmābhistato bhavān|| 159.52||
satyaṃ sucaritaṃ śuddhaṃ tapo 'asmābhirgaṇeśvara|
sahomaṃ yat tvayā sārdhaṃ drakṣyāma iha śaṃkaram|| 159.53||
evaṃ kapīndravadano vandamānāt tapodhanān|
sa satyān satyavacana idam āha śilādajaḥ|| 159.54||
-- -- -- mandaraṃ śailaṃ na kathaṃcit tyajedajaḥ|
ahaṃ tu kāryavān āgāṃ yuṣmākam imam āśramam|| 159.55||
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ giriputrī grahīṣyati|
nimantrayati vastatra sarvāñcharvo dvijottamān|| 159.56||
mānayanto bhavaṃ sarve sāmbam ambāpatiṃ drutam|
śvo gacchata taponityā mandaraṃ dharaṇīdharam|| 159.57||
tatra śarvam amarādhipaprabhuṃ tārakādhipavibhūṣaṇaṃ śivam|
drakṣyatheśam asurapramardanaṃ devatārtinikhilaṃ haran haram|| 159.58||
|| iti skandapurāṇe taruputrakagrahaṇe
brāhmaṇāmantraṇe
ūnaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 159.159||

ṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
āmantrya tānṛṣīn sarvān satyavīryayaśaḥśrutān|
nandī visarjitastaistu yayau sūryarathaṃ prati|| 160.1||
sa taṃ saptottamahayaṃ śakuntavarasārathim|
harājñayā raviṃ devam upāsarpata bhūtapaḥ|| 160.2||
sūryaraśmisahasreṣu tāpasān sa marīcipān|
apaśyat sa sukhāsīnāṃśchāyāsviva vihaṅgamān|| 160.3||
tataḥ sūryarathaṃ śīghram upetyārūṇasārathim|
so 'aṃśumālinam atriṃ ca atharvāṅgirasāvapi|| 160.4||
devānṛṣīn bhujaṅgāṃśca aśvāṃścāmantrayacchubhaḥ|
ādityāśvādibhirnandī rudrapiprīṣubhistadā|| 160.5||
tathetyuktopacakrāma sūryavāhādatha drutam|
devānṛṣīn bhujaṅgāṃśca tata āmantrya bhūtapaḥ|| 160.6||
sa vāyuriva śīghrastu garuḍo vā yathāṇḍajaḥ|
dhaneśabhavanaṃ nandī kailāsaṃ samupāgataḥ|| 160.7||
sa taṃ pāṇḍarameghābhaṃ kundendurajataprabham|
parvataṃ dhanadāvāsaṃ paśyamānaḥ prahṛsyata|| 160.8||
sa bhūteśo dhaneśasya girīśavacanaṃkaraḥ|
asasāda nagasyāgre bhavanaṃ kāñcanaṃ śubham|| 160.9||
kailāsāgre sanniviṣṭaṃ kailāsāgrasamatviṣam|
harmyaprāsādasampannaṃ sampannam iva bhāsitam|| 160.10||
pātākābhirdhvajaiścāpi kiṅkiṇījālamālibhiḥ|
hāsaiśca puraghoṣāṇāṃ sannāditam aharniśam|| 160.11||
bheryā paramaghorāṇāṃ vāditraśatanāditam|
ijyādhyayanasampannāstiṣṭhantyatra sabhāsadaḥ|| 160.12||
bhābhirjuṣṭāṃ sabhāṃ tasya tato rudrasabhāsadaḥ|
asasāda sa yatrāste munerviśravasaḥ sutaḥ|| 160.13||
tam ṛddhyā parayā yuktaṃ sevyamānaṃ śriyā tathā|
apaśyaddhanadaṃ nandī divyastrīgaṇasevitam|| 160.14||
śuktikarṇaṃ śuktikarṇairyakṣendrairabhisaṃvṛtam|
upagīyamānaṃ gandharvairekapiṅgāyatekṣaṇam|| 160.15||
maheśvarasakhatvena varadānamadena ca|
mādyantaṃ svarṇayā naddhamālayāmalalolayā|| 160.16||
dhanadaścāpi taṃ dṛṣṭvā śaṃkarānucaraṃ varam|
pūjayañchaṃkaraṃ somam utpapātāsanāddrutam|| 160.17||
svarṇādutpatamānastu āsanāddhanado babhau|
sāśokādiva puṣpāḍhyādudagrāt parvatādraviḥ|| 160.18||
tam utpatantam utpeturyakṣā yakṣapatiṃ drutam|
grahā yathā dīpyamānā dinahānau grahādhipam|| 160.19||
nandine sa tadārghaṃ ca pādyaṃ cāvedya vittadaḥ|
saputradāraḥ sāmātyaḥ praṇeme manasā haram|| 160.20||
tataḥ kathā bahuvidhāḥ kṛtvoddiśya maheśvaram|
papraccha dhanado nandiṃ cirasyāgamanaṃ kṛtam|| 160.21||
nandyuvāca|
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ giriputrī grahīṣyati|
nimantrayati tatra tvāṃ draviṇeśa maheśvaraḥ|| 160.22||
śvaḥ saputraḥ sadāraśca sānugaḥ sāpsarogaṇaḥ|
mandaraṃ yāhi vitteśa deveśaḥ prīyate tvayā|| 160.23||
evam āmantrya dhanadaṃ dhanadena visarjitaḥ|
yayau saṃyamanīṃ nandī yamasya yamasannibhaḥ|| 160.24||
sa yamaṃ dharmavaktāraṃ hartāraṃ prāṇināṃ prabhum|
sāgniṃ sadharmaṃ savyādhim apaśyadgaṇanāyakaḥ|| 160.25||
āyāntaṃ nandinaṃ dṛṣṭvā yamo bhūtaśatāvṛtaḥ|
pādābhyāṃ nandinaḥ so 'atha nipapāta tutoṣa ca|| 160.26||
rudrasyeva yamastasya pūjāṃ kṛtvā hyanuttamām|
papraccha nandinaṃ yatnāccirasyāgamanaṃ kṛtam|| 160.27||
nandyuvāca|
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ giriputrī grahīṣyati|
tatra tvāṃ sānugaṃ devo nimantrayati śaṃkaraḥ|| 160.28||
ye caiva viṣaye hyasmin nivasanti dvijātayaḥ|
tāṃścāmantrayate devaḥ sammānya bahumānataḥ|| 160.29||
kalyaṃ sa bhagavān kalyaḥ kālaḥ kālapriyaṃ girim|
mānayan prabhum īśānaṃ gantum arhasi mamdaram|| 160.30||
tathetyukto yamenātha taiścāgnisadṛśairdvijaiḥ|
sūryātmajagṛhānnandī śakralokaṃ tato gataḥ|| 160.31||
sukṛtīnāṃ tam āvāsaṃ vāsavaṃ lokam adbhutam|
viveśa tvaritaṃ nandī ditigarbhaṃ yathāhihā|| 160.32||
sa sudharmā sudharmāyāṃ sudharmam amarairvṛtam|
gāndharvam upaśṛṇvāṇaṃ nandī śakram apaśyata|| 160.33||
śakraśca nandinaṃ devaṃ devadevasya kiṃkaram|
harṣānnetrasahasrasthaṃ kṛtvā samyagapaśyata|| 160.34||
sa pūjāṃ rudrasadṛśīm avāpya tridaśeśvaram|
upāviśadameyātmā śakrābhyāse varāsane|| 160.35||
tam āsīnam upāsīnaḥ śatakraturarindamaḥ|
piban netrasahasreṇa na tṛptiṃ so 'abhyagaccata|| 160.36||
tato vṛtrabalāristaṃ nandinaṃ dinakṛtprabham|
paryapṛcchata harṣeṇa kiṃ cirādāgato bhavān|| 160.37||
ityuktaḥ sa tu devena devaḥ svarganivāsinā|
mandāravāsito 'avyagraḥ provāca kuliśādharaḥ|| 160.38||
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ giriputrī grahīṣyati|
tatra tvāṃ sāmaraṃ devo nimantrayati bhūtapaḥ|| 160.39||
dvijapūrvaṃ dvijā ye ca tavālayanivāsinaḥ|
saputradārāṃstāṃścāpi nimantrayati śaṃkaraḥ|| 160.40||
śvaḥ saputraḥ sadārastvaṃ devadevasya śāsanāt|
mandaraṃ gaccha deveśa girīśam abhinandaya|| 160.41||
tvayi yāte suraśreṣṭha aśokatarukotsave|
prītiṃ yāsyati deveśaḥ parāṃ suranarārttihā|| 160.42||
śitaśūladharaṃ pinākinaṃ girirājendrasutāpatiṃ prabhum|
praṇipatya maheśam ūrjitaṃ punarevaiṣyasi nākasaṃsadam|| 160.43||
|| iti skandapurāṇe viprāmantraṇe
ṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 160.160||

ekaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śakreṇa tu kṛtānujño nandī pramathanāyakaḥ|
brahmaṇo bhavanaṃ gantuṃ matiṃ dadhre mahādyutiḥ|| 161.1||
sa muhūrtānmahāvego mahāvega ivānilaḥ|
vairājaṃ bhavanaṃ prāptaścaturvaktrasya pārṣadaḥ|| 161.2||
hataklamāṃ sa tu sabhāṃ sabhāṃ merugireriva|
viveśa nandī tejasvī divākarakaro yathā|| 161.3||
tāṃ kathām iva citrārthāṃ citrārthairbahubhiryutām|
dadarśa sa sabhāṃ nandī bahvāścaryasamākulām|| 161.4||
tasyāṃ sabhāyām ālīnaṃ yatibhiḥ saha so 'adbhutam|
apaśyadabjajaṃ nandī devaiḥ pañcabhirāvṛtam|| 161.5||
vedārthaṃ bhāṣamāṇaṃ taṃ yatīnāṃ paripṛcchatām|
tāṃśca bhāṣyavidaḥ sarvāñchrutvā sādhviti vādinaḥ|| 161.6||
nandī pitāmahaṃ samyak pūjayāmāsa satvaram|
tataḥ pitāmahaḥ prāha nandinaṃ gaṇanāyakam|| 161.7||
kiṃ cirādāgato 'asīti sa ca taṃ pratyabhāṣata|
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ giriputrī grahīṣyati|| 161.8||
bhagavaṃstatra devastvāṃ nimantrayati śaṃkaraḥ|
imāṃśca tapasāgnyābhān savedān vedavādinaḥ|| 161.9||
nimantrayati deveśo yajñakoṭīnimantritaḥ|
yatibhiḥ saha sarvaistvaṃ mandaraṃ citrakandaram|| 161.10||
vraja mānada devānām ekam ājñāpayatyajaḥ|
ityevaṃ vacasāṃ kartā vacaḥ śrutvā sa nandinaḥ|| 161.11||
japyapriyam uvācedaṃ hṛṣṭarūpaḥ pitāmahaḥ|
nandīśvara vrajasva tvam avighnena śivena ca|| 161.12||
aham api āgamiṣyāmi ebhiḥ saha śivāntikam|
mokṣyate cāpyaśoko 'asau dakṣaśāpakṛtaṃ tamaḥ|| 161.13||
putrī himavato devī yaṃ grahīṣyati putrakam|
ityuktaḥ pratimānyeśam īśasya dayito 'agraṇīḥ|| 161.14||
brahmaṇo bhavanāt tūrṇaṃ kṣīrodam udadhiṃ yayau|
mālām iva samudrasya sa tu velām amālinīm|| 161.15||
gaṇeśvarasado mukhya āsasāda durutsahām|
sa velānilayān viprān bālakhilyāṃstapodhanān|| 161.16||
nānāniyamasaṃyuktānapaśyadgaṇanāyakaḥ|
vandamānaṃ tam ālokya gaṇeśaṃ suyaśāpatim|| 161.17||
āśīrbhiranukūlābhirnananduste tapodhanāḥ|
tapodhanānāṃ hṛṣṭānāṃ nandī madhyagato babhau|| 161.18||
grahāṇāṃ saumyarūpāṇāṃ yathā madhyagatoḍupaḥ|
atha pādyārghyadānena phaladānena caiva hi|| 161.19||
sampūjya nandinaṃ devaṃ bālakhilyāstam abruvan|
kutaścirasyāgamanam iha te pramathādhipa|
kacciddrakṣyāma deveśaṃ sāmbam ambāpatiṃ bhavam|| 161.20||
tato nandī dvijaśreṣṭhāñchreṣṭho vai pramathādhipaḥ|
sālāṅkāram idaṃ vākyam abravīddvijasaṃsadi|| 161.21||
mandare sāmbiko devo nehāgacchati śaṃkaraḥ|
iha cāgamanaṃ yanme tacchṛṇudhvaṃ tapodhanāḥ|| 161.22||
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ giriputrī grahīṣyati|
tatra vo gopatirdevo nimantrayati śaṃkaraḥ|| 161.23||
śvaḥ sarve dārasahitāḥ saśiṣyatanayāgnayaḥ|
mandaraṃ yāta viprāgryā mām ambāṃ cānugṛhṇata|| 161.24||
ityevaṃ nandinā prokto bālakhilyā maharṣayaḥ|
deve bhaktiprakarṣeṇa gaṇeśam idam abruvan|| 161.25||
bho nandin āgamiṣyāmaḥ śvaḥ prabhāte vayaṃ prabho|
parvataṃ yāhyavighnena mandaraṃ cārukandaram|| 161.26||
sa bālakhilyaiḥ praṇato 'abhipūjito nimantrya sarvāṃstripade dvijottamān|
punarnivṛtto 'abhijagāma mandaraṃ sa yatra devyā sahito 'avatiṣṭhate|| 161.27||
atha bhuvanapatiṃ patiṃ surāṇāṃ giritanayāmukhapaṅkajadvirepham|
dhanadavaradam etya bhūtanāthaṃ gaṇapatinātha idaṃ tadāvabhāṣe|| 161.28||
divi ca bhuvi ca ye caranti viprāḥ śamadamasaṃyamaśaucasattvayuktāḥ|
tripuradamana kālanāśa sarve tava vacanādvinimantritā mayā te|| 161.29||
|| iti skandapurāṇe taruputragrahaṇe viprāmantraṇaṃ nāma
ekaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 161.161||

dviṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
āmantriteṣu vipreṣu nārāyaṇapadatraye|
nandinyatha nivṛtte ca gaṇayūthapayūthape|| 162.1||
bhagavān kratukāmaghnaḥ pūṣṇo dantanipātanaḥ|
mālī maulī balī kālaḥ kāle vacanam abravīt|| 162.2||
ambike jagataḥ sarve brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇaḥ samāḥ|
āmantritā varārohe kuru yat te manogatam|| 162.3||
sa yatrāśokatarukaḥ putrakaste bhaviṣyati|
tatra sajjīkarotyannam annadaḥ piṅgalaḥ priye|| 162.4||
śvaḥ prabhāte yathā devi nandinā saha nandini|
yāmo 'aśokataroḥ pārśvaṃ tathā kuru girīndraje|| 162.5||
sākāśajālapātālaṃ jagajjanani tatra hi|
piṇḍīkṛtaṃ tvaddhitārthe bhaviṣyati gireḥ sute|| 162.6||
anena cāmantrayatā nandinā vai dvijottamān|
krāntaṃ trivikramākrāntaṃ nārāyaṇapadatrayam|| 162.7||
so 'aham asya varārohe vareṇye varadāyini|
varaṃ dāsyāmi varade yadi te rucitaṃ priye|| 162.8||
atha devī divo nāthaṃ ḍiṇḍimuṇḍeśvaraṃ haram|
avadadvaradaṃ kāntaṃ kāntaṃ candrārdhabhūṣaṇam|| 162.9||
ayaṃ nandīśvaro deva āvayoḥ paramo hitaḥ|
varakoṭīsahasrāṇi tvatto 'arhati na saṃśayaḥ|| 162.10||
varado hyasi lokānāṃ lokānām api ceśvaraḥ|
yadi tuṣṭo 'asi śailāderdiśasva pravaraṃ varam|| 162.11||
kṛttivāsāstato devo mūrdhnyupāghrāya nandinam|
uvāca pramatheśānaṃ vriyatām īpsito varaḥ|| 162.12||
tataḥ kapīndravadanaḥ sureśasadṛśadyutiḥ|
praṇamya śirasā prāha nandī śaṃkaravallabhaḥ|| 162.13||
prabhāvāt tava deveśa varadāsmyajarāmaraḥ|
bhogavān pūjitaḥ pūjyairdevadānavakinnaraiḥ|| 162.14||
kiṃ me vareṇa yo 'ahaṃ te varakoṭiprapūjitau|
paśyāmi caraṇau śarva sāmbasya pramathārcitau|| 162.15||
vareṇa tu mamānena gopate yadi tuṣyasi|
nityā bhavatu me bhaktistvayi sāmbe maheśvara|| 162.16||
śiṣṭānāṃ madviśiṣṭānāṃ gaṇānāṃ gaṇapādhipaḥ|
tvayā kṛto devavara kim ato 'anyat kariṣyasi|| 162.17||
ityevaṃ nandinaṃ devo bhāṣamāṇaṃ tadā natam|
prītyāpaśyadvirūpākṣaḥ śaśāṅkakṛtaśekharaḥ|| 162.18||
tatotpalanikāśena kareṇa bhagavān haraḥ|
pramṛjya prāha harṣeṇa harṣayan nandinaṃ bhṛśam|| 162.19||
bhaktimānasi me nandin sadāraṃ sagaṇāśrayam|
tāṃ ca bhaktiṃ puraskṛtya pārśvastho 'asi mayā kṛtaḥ|| 162.20||
satyāddharmāt tapodānādgobhyo vedebhya eva ca|
ebhyo me tvaṃ priyataraḥ sarvebhyo gaṇapeśvaraḥ|| 162.21||
prabhāte yaśca te nāma kīrtayiṣyati lokapa|
so 'aśvamedhasya ca phalaṃ samyagiṣṭasya lapsyate|| 162.22||
yaśca tvāṃ dveṣṭi vidviṣṭaḥ sa me dharmarato 'api hi|
yasya tvaṃ dayito 'asau me dayitastu bhavet sadā|| 162.23||
namo nandīśvarāyeti procya yaḥ svapsyate naraḥ|
tasya kuṣmāṇḍarājebhyo na bhaviṣyati vai bhayam|| 162.24||
ityevaṃ bruvatastasya nandīśvaraguṇastavam|
brahmaṇastanuratyugrā sandhyā samabhivartata|| 162.25||
sandhyākālaṃ tu kālajñaḥ kālaḥ kālanihā haraḥ|
upoḍhaṃ vīkṣya nṛttasya devaḥ kālam amanyata|| 162.26||
upaspṛśya tataḥ so 'adbhirapāṃ sraṣṭā trilokapaḥ|
anvāsta bhagavān sandhyāṃ lokasaṃsthāṃ nu pālayan|| 162.27||
prasāritakaro devo nyastajānukamaṇḍalaḥ|
prasāritakaro vyomni divākara ivābhavat|| 162.28||
japtvā tu paramaṃ japyaṃ trivedarasasambhavam|
bhavaḥ pranṛttyaccaturaścaturaṃ caturānanaḥ|| 162.29||
bhartāraṃ vīkṣya nṛtyantaṃ viṣaktakarapallavam|
sahadharmacarī devī bhartāraṃ sānvanṛtyata|| 162.30||
dampatī vīkṣya nṛtyantau sāṭṭahāsaṃ gaṇāgraṇīḥ|
prānṛtyata tato nandī devayoḥ prītim āvahan|| 162.31||
devam ambāṃ ca nṛtyantau nandinaṃ ca samīkṣya tu|
pramathā nīlameghābhāḥ pranṛttāstūryanisvanaiḥ|| 162.32||
tato bheryo jharjharāśca kikhirānakamaṇḍukāḥ|
āḍambarā ḍiṇḍimāśca śaṅkhāścaiva prasasvanuḥ|| 162.33||
muhurmuhuḥ sādhayate nṛttaṃ caturam ambikā|
nandī visṛjate hāsaṃ pramathā nedurulbaṇāḥ|| 162.34||
tattūryavaraśabdāḍhyaṃ śivāśanirivākulam|
sandhyāmukhaṃ babhau raudraṃ vaḍavāmukhasannibham|| 162.35||
nanṛturjahasuścānye jajapuśca tathāpare|
jaguścānye 'atimadhuraṃ gandharvā iva pārṣadāḥ|| 162.36||
tato 'ambaratalāpīḍe pūrṇabimbe 'atinirmale|
mṛgāṅke hyudite candre candrāvayavabhūṣaṇaḥ|| 162.37||
samāpya niyamaṃ devaḥ sāmbanandīśapārṣadaḥ|
virarāmotsavāt tasmāt pārvatīṃ cedam abravīt|| 162.38||
uṣitvā śarvarīm etāṃ śarvaryamitavikrame|
aśokatarukaṃ putraṃ tataḥ śvastvaṃ grahīṣyati|| 162.39||
dhāreyī sā sadarbhāyāṃ dhārāyāṃ dhāraṇīdharā|
suṣvāpa devavacanādekāṃ rātriṃ yatavratā|| 162.40||
tataḥ śatasahasrāṃśāvudite 'arke 'arkabhāvanaḥ|
umām āha prayāmeti yatrāśokaḥ sutaḥ sa te|| 162.41||
tato bhagavatī dhanyā dhanadā dhanadārcitā|
bhavam āha prayāmeti siñjamānavibhūṣaṇā|| 162.42||
pādacāreṇa bhagavān pādapaṃ pādapālayaḥ|
tam aśokataruṃ prāpa sanandī sāmbiko haraḥ|| 162.43||
sa tatra piṅgalaṃ yakṣaṃ piṅgalānalasannibham|
sādhayānaṃ dadarśānnam annadaṃ pramathaiḥ saha|| 162.44||
athātra bhakṣyabhojyasya coṣyalehyasya ca prabhuḥ|
so 'apaśyat parvataprakhyān rāśīn rāśividāṃ varaḥ|| 162.45||
sa sādhitaṃ tato dṛṣṭvā yakṣeṇānnaṃ pinākadhṛk|
praharṣam atulaṃ lebhe sāmbikaḥ saha nandinā|| 162.46||
tataḥ pitāmaho devaḥ saha devāpsaroragaiḥ|
tatrāgānmudito bhūtvā yatra sāmbo 'ambikāpatiḥ|| 162.47||
te praṇamya mahādevaṃ devāstenābhipūjitāḥ|
parivārya tadāśokam idam ūcurharāgrataḥ|| 162.48||
adyaprabhṛti vṛkṣo 'ayaṃ sarvataḥ sukhasaṃyutaḥ|
dakṣaśāpatamonmukto bhaviṣyati divaukasaḥ|| 162.49||
amaro jarayā tyaktaḥ sarvaduḥkhavivarjitaḥ|
sarvābharaṇapuṣpāḍhyaḥ sarvagandharasānvitaḥ|| 162.50||
sarvakāmapradaścaiva icchāpuṣpaphalastathā|
bhaviṣyati na saṃdeho devyāśca sudṛḍhaṃ priyaḥ|| 162.51||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
tato girīndratanayāṃ girīśaḥ praṇatārtihā|
paśyānnaparvatānetāniti provāca kāmadaḥ|| 162.52||
sā vīkṣya bhakṣyabhojyasya ucchrayān parvatopamān|
dṛḍhaṃ tutoṣa deveśā piṅgalasya guhāraṇiḥ|| 162.53||
sumālinaṃ yakṣavaraṃ piṅgalaṃ parvatātmajā|
yuyoja varadānena tām āha ca maheśvaraḥ|| 162.54||
devi sarvam idaṃ sajjaṃ bhakṣyaṃ bhojyaṃ tavottamam|
yat te manīṣitaṃ kāryaṃ tat kuruṣva kim āsyate|| 162.55||
tataḥ sātipramuditā divyāmbaranivāsinī|
manojavam anujñāpya śaṃkaraṃ bhuvaneśvaram|| 162.56||
daityaśokapradā devī tam aśokaṃ vibhāvarī|
alaṃcakāra sasnehā alaṃkāraiḥ pṛthagvidhaiḥ|| 162.57||
ātapatraṃ ca tasyāgre muktādāmāvabhāsitam|
ucchrāyamāsa girijā mayūrāṅgaruhaiḥ saha|| 162.58||
nānāvarṇena cāpyasya candanena sugandhinā|
ā mūlādakaroddevī varapaṅkāṅkitāṃ tanum|| 162.59||
jāmbūnadamayaiścāpi paṭṭairmaṇivirājitaiḥ|
sarvato bhūṣayāmāsa aśokatarukaṃ priyam|| 162.60||
tasya śākhāpraśākhāsu muktādāmāni pārvatī|
ābabandha sa tairbhāti nakṣatrairiva candramāḥ|| 162.61||
atha vāsoyugaiḥ śvetaistam aśokaṃ guhāraṇiḥ|
vāsayāmāsa lokānāṃ jananī putralālasā|| 162.62||
śrīveṣṭakaṃ nameruṃ ca guggulaṃ ghṛtam eva ca|
samavetaṃ tato dhūpaṃ dadau devavarapradā|| 162.63||
tataḥ śaṅkhaninādena devatūryaraveṇa ca|
baliṃ balavato bhāryā cakāra caratī tapaḥ|| 162.64||
tathārcayantyāstaṃ vṛkṣaṃ candrahārāmṛtaprabham|
stanābhyām asravat kṣīraṃ putrasnehābhisaṃgamāt|| 162.65||
umayā so 'arcito vṛkṣaḥ aśoko vanadīpakaḥ|
atīva śuśubhe tatra vasanta iva rūpavān|| 162.66||
nandinātha samānītān brāhmaṇān brahmaṇaḥ samān|
vācayāmāsa puṇyāhaṃ dattvā teṣāṃ yathepsitam|| 162.67||
tataḥ puṇyāhaghoṣānte āśīrvādasya cobhayoḥ|
anumānya patiṃ devī ṛṣīṃstānabravīt tu sā|| 162.68||
aputrā bhagavanto 'aham aśokatarukaṃ sutam|
imam adya grahīṣyāmi samanujñātum arhatha|| 162.69||
ityevaṃ bruvatīṃ devīṃ pārvatīṃ putralālasām|
samam ūcurdvijāḥ sarve iṣṭato gṛhyatām iti|| 162.70||
tataḥ śaṅkharavo divyaḥ sarvatūryaravānvitaḥ|
prababhau pūrayan sarvaṃ nārāyaṇapadatrayam|| 162.71||
vedānuccārayan viprā nṛtyantyapsarasāṃ gaṇaḥ|
neduśca pramathāḥ sarve sagandharvamahoragāḥ|| 162.72||
ṛtavaḥ ṣaṭ ca saṃhṛṣṭāḥ svaiḥ svaiḥ kusumasaṃcayaiḥ|
alaṃcakruraśokaṃ ca tacca daivatamaṇḍalam|| 162.73||
tat pravāditagāndharvaṃ pranṛttāpsarasāṃ gaṇam|
paśyanti hṛṣitā devā aśokatarukotsavam|| 162.74||
vādayan kacchapīṃ vīṇāṃ vīṇavādayatāṃ varaḥ|
nārado nṛtyate harṣādvātanunna ivānalaḥ|| 162.75||
tapodhanaiśca dhaninī devaiśca dhanadārcitā|
pūjyamānā babhau tatra raveriva yathā prabhā|| 162.76||
samāpya niyamaṃ sātha gṛhītvāśokaputrakam|
girīndratanayā bhāti dharā iva jalokṣitā|| 162.77||
atha nandīśvarādiṣṭāḥ pramathāste sahasraśaḥ|
adadan svāsanāni āśu viprāṇāṃ vipravatsalāḥ|| 162.78||
svarṇānāṃ rajatānāṃ ca sphaṭikānāṃ prabhāvatām|
pramathaiḥ kīryamāṇānām āsanānām abhūt svanaḥ|| 162.79||
meroḥ śikharavarṣāṇāṃ mahatī kuśajairiva| ?
tathāsanānyudvahatāṃ pramathānāṃ babhau ravaḥ|| 162.80||
varṣānnamṛṣṭākāmānāṃ (?)meghānāṃ stanatām iva|
skandhasthaiśca karasthaiśca uttamāṅgasthitairapi|| 162.81||
āsanaiḥ pramathā rejuḥ sārkāgnaya ivācalāḥ|
ānayantyapare tūrṇam apare dhārayantyuta|| 162.82||
pramathāste hṛṣṭarūpā hi āsanāni mahāsanāḥ|
ekaikayojanaśataṃ vistṛtāyojanāntaram|| 162.83||
asaṃsaktāsanā paṅktirnirmitā viśvakarmaṇā|
mandarasya śubhe pṛṣṭhe viprapaṅktyo viniḥsṛtāḥ|| 162.84||
tapanairnirgataiḥ sarvaiḥ samāmeghāsvasecanān?|| 162.85||
snāte patha iva dṛṣṭvā rejaturāsanabhūṣaṇāḥ| ?
sahasrapaṅktayastāstu mandare vistṛte girau|| 162.86||
dvijātīnanuliptāṃstu yakṣajambālamiśrakān| ?
saśekharān sasragdāmānanuhūya samodyatān?|| 162.87||
mandāraistu sasantānaiḥ pāribhadraistathaiva ca|
anilaiḥ sāṅganādāśca? rejurdevā iva dvijāḥ|| 162.88||
suślakṣṇaiśca sugandhaiśca gandhacūrṇaiḥ sapiñjaraiḥ|
avakīrṇāstato devairbhūmidevāḥ samantataḥ|| 162.89||
divyacandanapaṅkāṅkā divyacūrṇāvacūrṇitāḥ|
brāhmaṇā rejurekasthā ekasthā iva pāvakāḥ|| 162.90||
divyaṃ dhūpaṃ cārayitvā māmājñā (?) sarvaśaśca ha|
tataḥ sphaṭikasaṃkāśaṃ padmareṇurivārjitāḥ (?)|| 162.91||
hastaśaucaṃ muhūrtena dattaṃ śaṃkarakiṃkaraiḥ|
baddhakakṣāstataḥ śūrā baddhakakṣā iva dvipāḥ|
pariveṣṭum upakrāntāḥ pramathā brāhmaṇarṣabhān|| 162.92||
bhājanānyatha svarṇāni rājatasphāṭikāni ca|
muhūrtena dvijātīnāṃ dadurdevā vinītavat|| 162.93||
hṛtvā hṛtvā babhuu rekhaṃ daṇḍe vāri samaṇḍalam(?)|
bhakṣyabhojyānnapānāni daduḥ samyak samantataḥ|| 162.94||
arthavadyo haripurāsarāṭapurakānyapi|
netrasthaṃ hṛdayasthaṃ ca mukhasthaṃ hastasūcitam|| 162.95||
brāhmaṇānāṃ viduścaiva daduśca pramathādhipāḥ|
bhṛṅgāraiḥ kāñcanaiḥ kecit pānīyaṃ guṇavardhanam|| 162.96||
diśanto 'api carantyete pānīyam iti vādinaḥ|
apare candraraśmyābhaiścāmaraiḥ satsugandhibhiḥ|| 162.97||
āvījurbrāhmaṇān hṛṣṭāḥ pramathāstapasonilas(?)|
divyā devastriyaścaiva lokatrayanivāsinaḥ| 98||
ekaikaṃ brāhmaṇāṃstatra sevante vāsavaṃ yathā|
apsarovārasaṅghāśca sarvālaṃkārabhūṣitāḥ|| 162.99||
nanṛturdevacetāṃsi muṣṇantyaḥ sarvatodiśam|
viśvāvasūrnāradaśca tumburuḥ parvatastathā|| 162.100||
kustumburuḥ śāliśirāḥ parjanyo gaṇḍamaṇḍakaḥ|
citrāṅgadaścitrasenaścitraścitrarathastathā|| 162.101||
ete daivatagandharvā raktātodyā harapriyāḥ|
divyatāneṣu gāyanti geyaṃ manmathadīpanam|| 162.102||
namerurguggulūn miśro ghṛtadhārāvasecitaḥ|
dhūpaḥ saṃcāryate tatra pratīhārībhiruttamaḥ|| 162.103||
yadartham eṣa bhramati nārāyaṇapadatraye|
pūjyamānaḥ suraiḥ sendraiḥ śloko dhūpatrayāṅkanaḥ|| 162.104||
guggulośca namerośca ājyadhūpasya caiva ha|
tṛptiṃ na devā gacchanti priyāṇām iva darśanāt|| 162.105||
trayāṇām eva dhūpānāṃ jahurna pavanā gatim|
guggulośca namerośca ājyadhūpasya caiva ha|| 162.106||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā candramaulistu tarukotsavam īśvaraḥ|
pārvatīharṣado harṣaṃ pupoṣānuttamaṃ muhuḥ|| 162.107||
hṛṣyamāṇe paśupatau muhurvratapatau hare|
carācaraṃ paśupatau trailokyaṃ harṣaṇāyate|| 162.108||
pranṛttāpsaraso vāraṃ divyadhūpādhivāsitam|
ṛtubhiḥ kusumaiḥ kīrṇaṃ tat sado gaganāyate|| 162.109||
tataḥ śālyodanaṃ tūrṇaṃ -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
tena te 'amṛtakalpena sarva eva dvijottamāḥ|
bhakṣyabhojyānnapānena tatṛpurlokapūjitāḥ|| 162.110||
tataḥ śrutimukhaḥ puṇyo rākṣasāsuravejanaḥ|
puṇyāhaśabdaḥ prakṛto vipraistrailokyapūraṇaḥ|| 162.111||
tataḥ sāmbam aśokaṃ taṃ saharaṃ saha nandinā|
kusumākṣatasaṃyuktam āśīrbhirabhinandya ca|| 162.112|
mahāntaḥ susvanāḥ sarve brahmasūtrajaṭādharāḥ|
praṇamanto virūpākṣaṃ yayurviprā yathāgatam|| 162.113||
surāśca pūjitā dānairvākpradānaiśca śūlinā|
yathāgataṃ gatāḥ sarve parivārya śatakratum|| 162.114||
gaṇāśca gaṇapālena pūjitāḥ sagaṇādhipāḥ|
yathāvāsaṃ yayuḥ sarve harṣāduddhūtavāsasaḥ|| 162.115||
aho devyā hi saubhāgyam aho 'asyā vallabho haraḥ|
aho devasya devyarthaṃ sambhramo lakṣito hi naḥ|| 162.116||
yā naivaṃ dayitā bharturyatheśasya gireḥ sutā|
kathaṃ sā subhagā nāma strītvaṃ cāpi bibharti kim|| 162.117||
giriputryā kṛtaṃ manye tapaḥ paramabhāsvaram|
tapasābhijito yasyā varado vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 162.118||
aho strīṇāṃ balaṃ sūkṣmaṃ devairapi sudurjayam|
yena rudrasamā īśāḥ strīṇāṃ vaśyatvam āgatāḥ|| 162.119||
anye tānabruvaṃstatra mahātmāno gaṇādhipāḥ|
deva evaiṣa rūpeṇa bhāryā bhūtvāvatiṣṭhate|| 162.120||
māvamanyata devīṃ tāṃ yogāt kiṃ nāvabudhyatha|
ityevaṃ jalpamānāste anyonyena gaṇottamāḥ|
jagmuḥ svabhavanānyeva dīpyamānā yathāgnayaḥ|| 162.121||
devo 'api nandinā sārdhaṃ so 'ambayā cābhirūpayā|
aśokatarukasyādha upaviṣṭo 'ambikārcitaḥ|| 162.122||
tataḥ praṇamya varadaṃ somā somavibhūṣaṇam|
uvāca vacasāṃ yonirbhūtasaṃghapatiṃ patim|| 162.123||
sunirvṛttāsmi saṃvṛttā tripurāndhakasūdana|
yanmayāśokatarukaḥ putraḥ prakṛtakaḥ kṛtaḥ|| 162.124||
samastavyastam akhilaṃ trailokyaṃ lokabhāvana|
samāgataṃ tvatprabhāvānmama putratarūtsave|| 162.125||
nūnaṃ me sukṛtaṃ deva tapaḥ paramabhāsvaram|
labdho 'asi yanmayā deva sarvabhūtapatiḥ patiḥ|| 162.126||
devairyaccāpi muṣitam iṣṭaputraphalaṃ purā|
tanme sarvaṃ vyapagataṃ prāpyāśokataruṃ sutam|| 162.127||
matto dhanyatarā deva nāstyanyā tridive 'aṅganā|
patirvṛttapatirvīra yasyā me tvaṃ maheśvara|| 162.128||
bhavaṃ bhavānī prītyaivam uktvā muktāvalīdharā|
papāta padbhyāṃ devasya netrāsrāpūritekṣaṇā|| 162.129||
tām utthāpya girīśastu pariṣvajya ca pīḍitam|
niveśya urum urūbhyāṃ sasneham idam abravīt|| 162.130||
devī satī ca sādhvī ca sahadharmacarī ca me|
brahmaṇyā ca śaraṇyā ca tvaṃ me nityaṃ priyā priye|| 162.131||
akāryam api kāryaṃ hi ato devi mayā tava|
kiṃ punaryadyaśonmiśram īdṛśaṃ dharmasaṃyutam|| 162.132||
tarpitā brāhmaṇā devi devāśca sagaṇāstvayā|
gṛhītaḥ putrakaścāyaṃ tvayāśokataruḥ priye|| 162.133||
ehi devi gṛhān yāma sampūrṇaste manorathaḥ|
bhūyaḥ sutaṃ taṃ drakṣyāmaḥ stabakaiḥ samalaṃkṛtam|| 162.134||
ityuktā patinā sādhvī harṣapūrṇamukhekṣaṇā|
prāhedaṃ vacanaṃ tatra haritaṃ hariṇekṣaṇā|| 162.135||
hariṇākṣa sthitam iha amuṃ putra suputrakam|
gopāyasva hare yatnādgajāśvāccāṇḍajāṇḍapāt|| 162.136||
yadi vāpi bhavedeṣa stabakaiḥ samalaṃkṛtaḥ|
aśokaputrako mahyaṃ tadā māṃ draṣṭum arhasi|| 162.137||
iti saṃdiśya haritam udbhrāntahariṇekṣaṇā|
sāpāṅgacakṣurvikṣepaṃ kṛtvomā patinā saha|
viveśa sadanaṃ devī prabhevādityamaṇḍalam|| 162.138||
iti paśupatinā sahaiva devī sutam upagṛhya taruṃ hyaśokapotam|
pramuditagaṇamadhyagā viveśa svabhavanam eva tadā prahṛṣṭacittā|| 162.139||
|| iti skandapurāṇe aśokataruputragrahaṇe
dvisaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 162.162||

triṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
śārvaṃ tejaḥ samādāya vahniḥ kiṃ kṛtavāṃstadā|
kathaṃ skandaḥ samutpannaḥ kasmin sthāne mahādyutiḥ|| 163.1||
senāpatye kathaṃ cāsāvabhiṣiktaḥ surottamaiḥ|
kimartham abhiṣiktaśca kasmin deśe 'api vā prabho|| 163.2||
tārakaśca kathaṃ tena nihato raṇamūrdhani|
etadicchāmyahaṃ vettuṃ tvatprasādānmahāmune|| 163.3||
iti vijñāpito dhīmān vyāsenākliṣṭakarmaṇā|
provāca vadatāṃ śreṣṭhaḥ pitāmahasutastadā|| 163.4||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atra trailocanaṃ tejaḥ sutasaṃkalpasambhavam|
na dhārayitum utsehe dīptimānapi pāvakaḥ|| 163.5||
dāhātmako 'api bhūtānāṃ dahyamānaḥ sa tejasā|
gaṅgām abhyarthayāmāsa dhāraṇe tasya tejasaḥ|| 163.6||
sā tenābhyarthitā devī hutāśena trilokagā|
evam astviti sāśaṅkam uvāca madhurasvarā|| 163.7||
tat tejo devadevasya tejasvī havyavāhanaḥ|
tadā saṃkrāmayāṃcakre gaṅgāyāṃ yogamāyayā|| 163.8||
jñātvāpi durdharaṃ tat sā pratipede varānanā|
arthipraṇayanirbhaṅgadoṣabhītā saridvarā|| 163.9||
atha sā kṣipram abhavanmantharālasagāminī|
prabhāvāt tejasastasya śyāmonmukhapayodharā|| 163.10||
bhinnāñjanarucā tanvyā romarājyā rarāja sā|
ghanarājyā ghanāpāye lekhevānuṣṇadīdhiteḥ|| 163.11||
jagāma ca tadā glāniṃ kiṃcidāviplutekṣaṇā|
nopalebhe tadā devī ratiṃ śayyāsaneṣu ca|| 163.12||
amṛtasyandibhiḥ śītaiḥ spṛṣṭāpi śaśinaḥ karaiḥ|
mamlau sā tejasā tena dahyamānā tadānaghā|| 163.13||
-- -- -- -- $E$-- -- $E$-- -- śarastambābhirājite|
sotsasarja tadā tejo harasyograṃ śubhe 'ahani|| 163.14||
śaramadhyāt samabhavadbālo bālaparākramaḥ|
ṣaḍvaktro dvādaśabhujaḥ sūryakoṭisamadyutiḥ|| 163.15||
samidhya vidhinā tatra pāvakaṃ pāvakatviṣaḥ|
viśvāmitrastadā cakre jātakarma sujanmanaḥ|| 163.16||
kṛttikāstaṃ tadā dṛṣṭvā prasnutorupayodharāḥ|
ājagmurantikaṃ tasya -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 163.17||
upatasthuśca taṃ vedāḥ sopavedāḥ sasaṃgrahāḥ|
kalā vidyāśca nikhilā lakṣmīrmedhā sarasvatī|| 163.18||
kāntirdharmo dayā kṣāntirdhṛtirdhairyaṃ parākramaḥ|
yogastejo balaṃ prajñā sthitigāmbhīryasatkriyāḥ|| 163.19||
athāto dhanurādāya divyam adbhutavikramaḥ|
sandhāya līlayā bāṇaṃ sa mumoca girau -- --|| 163.20||
prodbhinnaṃ sahasā tena bhūbhṛtaḥ śikharottamam|
papātāśu paritrastabhītodbhrāntavihaṅgamam|| 163.21||
taddṛṣṭvā mahadāścaryaṃ sattvānāṃ tannivāsinām|
vismayaśca bhayaṃ caiva yugapat sambabhūvatuḥ|| 163.22||
atha prekṣya bhayaṃ tasmādātmano balasūdanaḥ|
mātR̥ḥ sampreṣayāmāsa vināśāyāmitadyuteḥ|| 163.23||
āgatya mātarastatra dṛṣṭvā taṃ tejasāṃ nidhim|
tam eva śaraṇaṃ jagmustattejohṛtacetasaḥ|| 163.24||
ājagāma tataḥ kruddhaḥ saha vrātairdivaukasām|
airāvatagajaskandham ārūḍhaḥ pākaśāsanaḥ|| 163.25||
āgacchataḥ surān dṛṣṭvā nanādoccairmahādyutiḥ|
abhyadravacca saṃkruddhaḥ siṃho mattān gajāniva|| 163.26||
babhūvustena nādena muhurmūḍhā divaukasaḥ|
abhūdairāvaṇasyāpi madadhvaṃsaḥ kapolayoḥ|| 163.27||
arcīṃṣi ca pradīptāni visasarja sahasraśaḥ|
trilocanasutasteṣāṃ surāṇāṃ suradarpahā|| 163.28||
arcirbhirhatakāntīni mukhānyasuravidviṣām|
babhūvurhimadagdhāni sarojāni saraḥsviva|| 163.29||
atha vajraṃ samādāya jvalitaṃ jvalanadyuteḥ|
roṣādātāmranetrānto visasarja śatakratuḥ|| 163.30||
tena vajraprahāreṇa sa dvimūrtistadābhavat|
dvābhyām api ca mūrtibhyām abhyadhāvat purandaram|| 163.31||
atha darpaṃ vihāyāśu praṇeme pākaśāsanaḥ|
tejasāṃ nidhaye tasmai prāha caivaṃ vinirjitaḥ|| 163.32||
gṛhāṇa rājyam apyetat prārthanīyaṃ manasvinām|
tvam eva yukto lokānāṃ pālane pāvakātmaja|| 163.33||
satsvapyanyeṣu tejassu tamasāṃ vinihantṛṣu|
agnāveva haviḥ puṇyaṃ hūyate -- -- -- -- --|| 163.34||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
prāha prabhavatāṃ śreṣṭho vihasya vibudhādhipam|| 163.35||
śādhi śakra tvam evedaṃ rājyaṃ ciram abhīpsitam|
anena bahudoṣeṇa nāham arthī purandara|| 163.36||
niśāmya tadvacaḥ śrīmān skandasyākliṣṭacetasaḥ|
arthavadvacanaṃ ślakṣṇaṃ punarāha śacīpatiḥ|| 163.37||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 163.38||
darśaya no vicitrāṇi kāryajātānyanekadhā|
saṃgatāni vibhinnāni -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 163.39||
evam uktavati prāha sambhavatyanaladyutiḥ|
snigdhagambhīrayā vāca smitapūrvam idaṃ vacaḥ|| 163.40||
na vicālayituṃ cetaḥ śakra śaktā haṭhānmama|
na vāri saritāṃ patyuralātaiḥ sampratapyate|| 163.41||
rājyaṃ rājīvapatrākṣa na jātu manasāpyaham|
doṣāṇāṃ nityam āvāsaṃ kāmaye pākaśāsana|| 163.42||
tasya tadvacanaṃ śrutvā punarvaktum iyeṣa saḥ|
sudhāniṣyandibhiḥ skandaṃ snapayanniva locanaiḥ|| 163.43||
ākare tejasāṃ ślāghye naitaccitraṃ tvayi prabho|
śaktā evaṃ na sajjante bhogeṣu sumahatsvapi|| 163.44||
senāpatye 'abhiṣicyasva surāṇām arthasiddhaye|
vapuḥ (?) saṃmānayāmīha nāham ājñāpaye vibho|| 163.45||
atha tadvacanaṃ śrutvā puruhūtaṃ mahābhujaḥ|
dvādaśākṣaḥ sahasrākṣam idam āhoruvikramaḥ|| 163.46||
mama prabhavati śrīmān lokānāṃ prabhuravyayaḥ|
ananyabhūrameyātmā vṛṣaketuḥ purandara|| 163.47||
tam ārādhya prabhuṃ bhaktyā gṛhāṇājñāṃ śatakrato|
tām ahaṃ pratipatsyāmi yām asau dāsyati prabhuḥ|| 163.48||
tasyābhiprāyam ājñāya devadevo vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
ājagāma sapatnīko didṛkṣustanayaṃ tadā|| 163.49||
svāhayā sahito vahnirgaṅgā ca saritāṃ varā|
kṛttikāśca susaṃhṛṣṭāḥ śvetaṃ śikhariṇāṃ varam|| 163.50||
yugapat te tadā tatra śvetasya śikharottame|
cintayāmāsurāyāntaḥ kaṃ nu skando 'abhiyāsyati|| 163.51||
atha teṣām abhiprāyaṃ jñātvā matimatāṃ varaḥ|
ṣoḍhā samabhavat skando yogīśo balavat tadā|| 163.52||
skando 'abhyagānmahādevaṃ viśākho himavatsutām|
naigameṣo yayau gaṅgāṃ vahniṃ śākho mahādyutiḥ|| 163.53||
svāhāṃ jagāma saṃhṛṣṭaḥ kākapakṣadharo guhaḥ|
kṛttikāḥ ṣaṇmukhasśrīmān vegādabhisasāra ca|| 163.54||
manorathān sa sarveṣāṃ devadevātmajaḥ prabhuḥ|
yugapadyoginām īśaḥ pūrayāmāsa mūrtibhiḥ|| 163.55||
atha tasmai dadau śambhurastragrāmaṃ caturvidham|
sudhākaṇaparisrāvi cūḍāratnaṃ ca pārvatī|| 163.56||
svamanonirmalāṃ gaṅgā viśuddhām amṛtodbhavām|
ekāvaliṃ dadau tasmai guhāyotphullalocanā|| 163.57||
dviṣatprāṇaharāṃ gurvīm amoghāṃ havyavāhanaḥ|
arciṣmatīṃ dadau cāsmai śaktiṃ śaktāya sūnave|| 163.58||
patākāṃ mahatīṃ raktāṃ jvalatpāvakasaprabhām|
kiṅkiṇīnāditāṃ divyāṃ prādāt svāhā mahātmane|| 163.59||
supuṇyagandhām utphullāṃ svarajaḥparipiñjarām|
kṛttikāśca dadustasmai mālām añcitakesarām|| 163.60||
athājagmuḥ surāḥ sarve pitāmahapuraḥsarāḥ|
śvetādreḥ śikharaṃ ramyaṃ vṛṣaketuṃ didṛkṣavaḥ|| 163.61||
tān āgatān samaṃ sarvāṃstadā tatra divaukasaḥ|
dṛṣṭyā sambhāvayāmāsa mahādevaḥ prasannayā|| 163.62||
praṇamya devadeveśaṃ labdhvānujñāṃ divaukasaḥ|
śilāsu śaśigaurīṣu niṣeduramitaujasaḥ|| 163.63||
prottuṅgaśikharaḥ śveto dyutimānapi bhūdharaḥ|
tejasāṃ sannipātena babhūva dyutimattaraḥ|| 163.64||
atha pracoditaḥ sarvairvibudhairvibudhādhipaḥ|
vyajñāpayanmahādevaṃ praṇamya vadatāṃ varaḥ|| 163.65||
tārakākhyena no lakṣmīrāmṛṣṭā prasabhaṃ prabho|
vajraṃ vakṣaḥsthale tasya kaṭhine kuṇṭhatāṃ yayau|| 163.66||
cakraṃ hareḥ sahasrāraṃ jvalitaṃ jvalitaujasaḥ|
āsādya mṛdutāṃ bheje kaṇṭhaṃ tasyāmaradviṣaḥ|| 163.67||
daṇḍo vaivasvatasyāpi pradīptānalabhāsvaraḥ|
alātam iva toyaughe nirvāṇo dānavorasi|| 163.68||
samare ripusurvāro mahāpāśaḥ pracetasaḥ|
tasya kaṇṭhe samabhavanmantreṇeva vaśīkṛtaḥ|| 163.69||
utpāṭya prasabhaṃ tena nandane kalpapādapāḥ|
niveśitā yathākāmaṃ svagṛhodyānabhūmiṣu|| 163.70||
samīpe tasya sāśaṅkastālavṛntāyate 'anilaḥ|
svapuṣpanikarairbhītā ṛtavastam upāsate|| 163.71||
havirbhuji hutaṃ havyam ācchinatti balādasau|
miṣatāṃ sarvadevānāṃ devadeva diteḥ sutaḥ|| 163.72||
abhiṣicya surāḥ skandaṃ senāpatye mahādyutim|
jetum icchanti daityendraṃ prasādāt tava śaṃkara|| 163.73||
evaṃ vijñāpitastatra vajriṇā vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|
dadāvanujñāṃ skandāya senāpatyābhiṣecane|| 163.74||
atha vibudhasamūhairvandito vandanīyo madanatanuvihantā bālacandrārdhamauliḥ|
tanayam abhisamīkṣya snehasamphullanetraḥ śaśikiraṇasitādrerāśu so 'antarbabhūva|| 163.75||
|| iti skandapurāṇe skandābhiṣekānujñāne
trisaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 163.163||

catuḥṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atha te skandam ādāya surā brahmapuraḥsarāḥ|
samantapañcakaṃ puṇyam ājagmuramitaujasaḥ|| 164.1||
tasmiṃstīre sarasvatyāḥ prāgudakpravaṇe same|
vistīrṇe śvabhrapāṣāṇakaṇṭakoṣaravarjite|| 164.2||
skandasya paritaḥ sarve tadā saṃhṛṣṭacetasaḥ|
niṣeduste suraśreṣṭhā jvalitānalavarcasaḥ|| 164.3||
tat puṇyam amaraiḥ pṛktaṃ sthānaṃ puṇyataraṃ punaḥ|
abhūdgāṅgairivāmbhobhiḥ sametaṃ yāmunaṃ payaḥ|| 164.4||
ājagāmātha taṃ deśaṃ kṣitirmūrtimatī tadā|
skandābhiṣeke saṃjāte harṣasamphullalocanā|| 164.5||
athāsau kṣipram abhavaddeśaḥ kanakabālukaḥ|
vicitraḥ paritaścitraiḥ sphuradratnagabhastibhiḥ|| 164.6||
adhyāsata mahātmāno yaṃ deśam apamatsarāḥ|
nirastaduritaḥ so 'abhūt tatra teṣāṃ vibhūtibhiḥ|| 164.7||
atha siṃhāsanaṃ divyaṃ śātakumbhaṃ susaṃskṛtam|
gṛhītvā giribhiḥ sārdham ājagāma himālayaḥ|| 164.8||
ratnairoṣadhibhirgandhaiḥ pūrṇān puṇyaiśca vāribhiḥ|
ādāya kalaśān haimān phullāmburuhamālinaḥ|| 164.9||
udanvantaḥ susambhrāntāḥ pracalanmaṇikuṇḍalāḥ|
ājagmustvaritāstatra hāravibhrājitorasaḥ|| 164.10||
gaṅgā ratnamayāṃścārūn kalaśān sphuritatviṣaḥ|
haimāmbujakṛttottsaṃsān pūrṇān paramavāriṇā|| 164.11||
gṛhītvā saha sarvābhiḥ saridbhiḥ saritāṃ varā|
ājagāma tadā harṣāt praskhalantī sameṣvapi|| 164.12||
abhiṣecanikān kumbhān grāhayitvā susaṃskṛtān|
nānāratnaprabhodyotapratiraktārkadīdhitīn|| 164.13||
devībhiḥ saha bahvībhirājagāma divaukasām|
ākrāmantīva tejāṃsi tejasā svena pārvatī|| 164.14||
adbhiḥ paramapuṇyābhiḥ pūrṇān ratnāṃśumālinaḥ|
kalaśān sphāṭikāñchubhrān grāhayitvā susaṃskṛtān|| 164.15||
mukuṭaṃ ca mahacchlāghyaṃ dīptimaccāruvigraham|
nānāratnavicitrāṃśusamūhasphuritodaram|| 164.16||
hāraṃ ca nirmalaṃ śuddhaṃ śaśāṅkakiraṇatviṣam|
kāntaṃ muktāvitānaṃ ca cetohāri sunirmalam|| 164.17||
abhyāgamat tadā tatra prahṛṣṭo yādasāṃ patiḥ|
dānavādhipamātaṅgaviṣāṇollikhitāṅgadaḥ|| 164.18||
ratnāṅgadāni cārūṇi dyutimanti dhaneśvaraḥ|
samādāyābhyagāt sāraṃ sarvāsām iva sampadām|| 164.19||
niśākarāṃśugaurāṇi dīrghāṇi rucimanti ca|
ādāya ratnadaṇḍāni cāmarāṇi mahādyutiḥ|| 164.20||
vaivasvato 'api sampūrṇaśaraccandrāṃśunirmalam|
prodvahan vakṣasā hāram ājagāma tadantikam|| 164.21||
ātapatrāpadeśena dadau tasmai mahātmane|
phalaṃ surādhipatyasya samagram iva vāsavaḥ|| 164.22||
bhūṣayantastarūṃstatra khapuṣpanikarodgamaiḥ|
ṛtavastaṃ tadā deśam ājagmustuṣṭacetasaḥ|| 164.23||
arundhatī śacī svāhā sinīvālī girīndrajā|
aditirdevamātā ca niśā sānumatiḥ kuhūḥ|| 164.24||
hrīḥ śrīḥ puṣṭirdiśo dyauśca sutāḥ sarvāḥ prajāpateḥ|
rākā ca dhiṣaṇā caiva surabhirdevayoṣitaḥ|| 164.25||
oṣadhyo mūrtimatyaśca kauśikī vanadevatā|
ahaḥ kāṣṭhā muhurtāśca māsāḥ saṃvatsaraḥ kalāḥ|| 164.26||
airāvaṇaḥ supratīko vāmanaḥ kumudo 'añjanaḥ|
puṣpadanto mahāpadmaḥ sārvabhaumaśca diggajāḥ|
ābhiṣecanikaṃ sarvam upaninyurmahātmanaḥ|| 164.27||
jvalitavahnisamānaruco jaṭāḥ pariniyamya himācalavāsinaḥ|
tam abhijagmurudīrṇatapobalā munivarā muditā dahanātmajam|| 164.28||
vibudhasadmaratā jvalitaujasastridaśavanditapādasaroruhāḥ|
ṛṣigaṇāstvaritābhiyayurguhaṃ niyamitorjitanityatapaḥkriyāḥ|| 164.29||
samuditā muditotsukamānasāḥ kamalayonisutāśca mahaujasaḥ|
tam abhijagmurudārayaśobhṛtastrinayanātmajam agryabalodayam|| 164.30||
abhiyayustvaritā bhujageśvarāḥ svaphaṇiratnamarīcivitāninaḥ|
viṣabhṛto 'apyatisaumyavapurdharā dahanasūnum alaṅghyaparākramam|| 164.31||
upayayurgaruḍāśca vimatsarā bhujagarājasurūḍhabalodayāḥ|
drutataraṃ taruṇārkasamadyutiṃ pavanavegavijihmitapādapāḥ|| 164.32||
nanṛturāyatalolavilocanā vividhabhāvavilāsarasānvitāḥ|
paramayauvanarūpaguṇānvitāḥ pramuditāḥ parito 'apsaraso 'alasāḥ|| 164.33||
vividhapuṣparajoruṇamūrtayaḥ surabhigandhavahā vivavustadā|
virajaso 'atitarāṃ mṛduvṛttayo vibudhacittasukhāśca samīraṇāḥ|| 164.34||
ābhiṣecanikaṃ kṛtvā vidhiṃ tasya bṛhaspatiḥ|
samidhya jvalanaṃ samyak cacāra śarajanmanaḥ|| 164.35||
āśīrbhirāśiṣāṃ dhāma samāśliṣya śivātmajam|
stutyaṃ stutibhiragryābhistuṣṭuvurmunayastadā|| 164.36||
maṅgalāni jagustasya gandharvā nāradaśca yaḥ|
pratisārya tadā vīṇāṃ tāraṃ raktam anākulam|| 164.37||
atha taṃ dakṣiṇe pāṇau gṛhītvā kṛtamaṅgalam|
guruḥ siṃhāsane tasmin prāṅmukhaṃ saṃnyaveśayat|| 164.38||
anāhatāstadā vyomni neduruccairdivaukasām|
bhṛśaṃ dundubhayaścitrāḥ samyak cetopahāriṇaḥ|| 164.39||
mattadvirephasaṃgītāḥ svakiñjalkāruṇatviṣaḥ|
puṇyagandhā vicitrāśca nipetuḥ puṣpavṛṣṭayaḥ|| 164.40||
caturbhirvadanaiḥ skandaṃ stuvan gīrbhiḥ prajāpatiḥ|
ādade kalaśaṃ pūrvaṃ pūrṇaṃ puṇyena vāriṇā|| 164.41||
samādhāyāmbaraṃ pītaṃ tato viṣṇuḥ samādade|
kalaśaṃ kaustubhamaṇeḥ parāmṛṣṭaṃ gabhastibhiḥ|| 164.42||
tataḥ keyūraratnāṃśukhacitaṃ pākaśāsanaḥ|
uttarīyaṃ niyamyāśu jagrāha kalaśaṃ tadā|| 164.43||
nibadhya śaśilekhāṅkā jaṭā jvalanapiṅgalāḥ|
jagṛhuḥ kalaśān rudrā bhujaṅgakṛtakaṅkaṇāḥ|| 164.44||
bibhrato 'api parāṃ dīptiṃ sukhasaṃsparśamūrtayaḥ|
ādityā jagṛhuḥ pūrṇān kalaśān puṇyavāribhiḥ|| 164.45||
vasavo 'api surendrārigajadantakṣatorasaḥ|
ādaduḥ kalaśāṃstatra pūrṇān puṇyena vāriṇā|| 164.46||
aśvināvapi puṇyābhiḥ pūrṇāvadbhiḥ susaṃskṛtau|
ādadāte tadā kumbhau haimau ratnāṃśumālinau|| 164.47||
kumbhān ādadire tatra jvalanā jvalitatviṣaḥ|
haimāmburuhasaṃchannāṃścitrān ratnagabhastibhiḥ|| 164.48||
nāgagandharvarājāno lokapālā marudgaṇāḥ|
ṛṣayo bālakhilyāśca pitaraḥ patageśvarāḥ|| 164.49||
dharmo dhātā vidhātā ca kālo mṛtyurvasundharā|
sandhyā kāntirdhṛtirmedhā kīrtirlakṣmīḥ sarasvatī|| 164.50||
samudrāḥ sarito vedāstīrthāni girayo grahāḥ|
kumbhān ādadire tatra pūrṇān paramavāriṇā|| 164.51||
atha te hṛṣṭamanasaḥ prahṛṣṭaṃ pāvakātmajam|
abhyaṣiñcaṃstadā sarve senāpatye mahaujasam|| 164.52||
jayaśabdaṃ tataścakruḥ samaṃ sarve divaukasaḥ|
jayinaḥ śarvaputrasya ṛṣayaśca samāgatāḥ|| 164.53||
jagrāha maghavā tasya śvetam ātapavāraṇam|
sarvaratnaprabhāvrātavitānapariveṣavat|| 164.54||
dudhuvuścāmarairdīrghaiḥ śaraccandrāṃśunirmalaiḥ|
parito ratnadaṇḍaiśca lokapālā mahādyutim|| 164.55||
amṛtādutthitaṃ divyam upanītaṃ pracetasā|
maulim āropayāṃcakre sutasya himavatsutā|| 164.56||
hemāvadāte vistīrṇe śaśāṅkakiraṇadyutim|
tasya vakṣaḥsthale hāraṃ babandha saritāṃ varā|| 164.57||
hāreṇālaṃkṛtaṃ vakṣaḥ kiṃ tu hāro guhorasā|
iti tatra vitarko 'abhūt tadā vibudhasaṃsadi|| 164.58||
ābabandha mahābāhoraṅgadāni svalaṃkṛtā|
bhujeṣu pāraṇālānastambhapīneṣvarundhatī|| 164.59||
dīptimān pāvakasutastadābhūddīptimattaraḥ|
sarpiṣā hūyamānena jvalito 'agnirivādhvare|| 164.60||
dadau tasmai caturvaktraḥ prabhuḥ prīto mahātmane|
mahāpāriṣadāñchūrān balinaḥ kāmarūpiṇaḥ|| 164.61||
ghaṇṭākarṇaṃ suraktākṣaṃ nandiṣeṇaṃ ca durjayam|
caturthaṃ balināṃ śreṣṭhaṃ khyātaṃ kumudamālinam|| 164.62||
dadau sthāṇurmahāvīryaṃ mahāpāriṣadaṃ kratum|
sampravṛtte tadā ghore saṃgrāme tārakāmaye|| 164.63||
kruddho jaghāna daityānāṃ yo yutāni caturdaśa|
vibudhāśca dadustasmai senāṃ nairṛtasaṃkulām|| 164.64||
daityayakṣakṣayakarīm ajeyāṃ viśvarūpiṇīm|
dadau vaivasvatastasmai mahāpāriṣadāvubhau|| 164.65||
unmāthaṃ ca pramāthaṃ ca mahāvīryaparākramau|
subhrājaṃ bhāsvaraṃ caiva dadau sūryo 'anuyāyinau|| 164.66||
kārttikeyāya saṃhṛṣṭo raṇe paramadurjayau|
kailāsaśikharākārau śvetasraganulepanau|| 164.67||
candramāpi dadau tasmai maṇiṃ sumaṇim eva ca|
jvālājihvaṃ tathā jyotim ātmajāya vibhāvasuḥ|| 164.68||
dadau paramasamprītaḥ śatrusainyanibarhaṇau|
parighaṃ paṭahaṃ bhīmaṃ dahātidahanau tathā|| 164.69||
aṃśo 'apyanucarān pañca dadau skandāya dhīmate|
utkrośaṃ satvaraṃ caiva vajradaṇḍadharāvubhau|| 164.70||
sutāya devadevasya dadau prītaḥ śatakratuḥ|
cakraṃ vikramakaṃ caiva saṃkramaṃ cātidurjayam|| 164.71||
dadau jvalanaputrāya viṣṇuḥ prīto mahāyaśāḥ|
vardhanaṃ nandanaṃ caiva sarvavidyāntagāvubhau|| 164.72||
skandāya dadatuḥ prītāvaśvinau ca mahābalau|
kunduraṃ kumudaṃ cograṃ kumudaṃ ca (?) mahābalam|| 164.73||
ḍambarāḍambarau cobhau dadau dhātāgnisūnave|
vakrānuvakrau balinau meṣāsyau durjayau raṇe|| 164.74||
dadau tvaṣṭā mahāmāyau skandāyānucarāvubhau|
suvrataṃ satyasandhaṃ ca dadau mitro mahātmane|| 164.75||
suprabhaṃ ca mahāmāyaṃ śubhakarmāṇam eva ca|
prādādvidhātā skandāya śatrupakṣaniṣūdanau|| 164.76||
pālintakaṃ mahāvīryaṃ kālakaṃ ca mahābalam|
dadau pāriṣadau pūṣā skandāyāmitatejase|| 164.77||
balaṃ cātibalaṃ caiva mahākāyau mahābalau|
pradadau kārttikeyāya vāyuḥ prīto mahātmane|| 164.78||
ghasaṃ ca praghasaṃ caiva timivaktrau mahodarau|
dadau jvalanaputrāya varuṇaḥ pāśadhāriṇau|| 164.79||
suvarcasaṃ mahāvīryaṃ tathā cāpyativarcasam|
himavān pradadau tasmai skandāyātibalāvubhau|| 164.80||
kāñcanaṃ ca mahāmāyaṃ tathā jīmūtamālinam|
dadāvanucarau merurubhau jvalanasūnave|| 164.81||
sthiraṃ cātisthiraṃ caiva tathā pariṣadāvubhau|
punardadau mahāmeruḥ skandāyāmitatejase|| 164.82||
ucchṛṅgaṃ ca viśṛṅgaṃ ca śilāpāṣāṇayodhinau|
prādādvindhyo mahāsattvau skandāya jvalitaujase|| 164.83||
saṃgrahaṃ vigrahaṃ caiva samudraśca gadādharau|
pradadau kārttikeyāya mahāpāriṣadau tadā|| 164.84||
unmādaṃ puṣpadantaṃ ca śaṅkukarṇaṃ ca durjayam|
mahāvīryān mahāsattvān prādāt putrāya pārvatī|| 164.85||
jayaṃ mahājayaṃ caiva dadurnāgā mahātmane|
dadau ca paramaprītaḥ skandāya vṛṣavāhanaḥ|| 164.86||
bahūn pāriṣadāñchūrān samare durjayān paraiḥ|
gajakarṇaṃ nikumbhaṃ ca padmaṃ kumudam eva ca|| 164.87||
sanandaṃ dvādaśabhujaṃ tathā kṛṣṇopakṛṣṇakau|
kṛtagrīvaṃ kapiskandhaṃ kāñcanākṣaṃ jalandhamam|| 164.88||
akṣisantardanaṃ kuṇṭhaṃ pārśvagrīvaṃ mahodaram|
ekākṣaṃ dvādaśabhujam ekapādaṃ mahājaṭam|| 164.89||
sahasrabāhuṃ vikacaṃ vyāghrāsyaṃ kṣitikampanam|
pṛṣṭhavaktraṃ sunāmānaṃ pārśvānanamahānanau|| 164.90||
parisrutaṃ kokanadaṃ priyamālyānulepanam|
ajodaraṃ gajaskandhaṃ skandhākṣaṃ śatalocanam|| 164.91||
jvālājihvaṃ karālaṃ ca śitakeśaṃ tatodaram|
aṣṭajihvaṃ caturdaṃṣṭraṃ meghanādaṃ pṛthūdaram|| 164.92||
vidyudakṣaṃ dhanurvaktraṃ jaraṭhaṃ mārutāśanam|
udarākṣaṃ jhaṣākṣaṃ ca vajranābhaṃ ca suprabham|| 164.93||
samudravegaṃ gokarṇaṃ śailakampanam eva ca|
patrameṣaṃ prabāhuṃ ca tathā nandopanandakau|| 164.94||
dhūmraṃ śvetaṃ kaliṅgaṃ ca siddhārthaṃ varadaṃ tathā|
priyakaṃ gardabhāsyaṃ ca gonardaṃ bhūtatāpanam|| 164.95||
ānandaṃ ca pramodaṃ ca svastikaṃ dhruvakaṃ tathā|
kṣepavāhaṃ sujātaṃ ca siddhayātraṃ mahāvaram|| 164.96||
govrajaṃ kanakāpīḍaṃ mahāpārśvaṃ mahodaram|
gāyanaṃ hasanaṃ caiva bāṇakhaḍgadharaṃ prabhum|| 164.97||
vaitāliṃ cātitāliṃ ca tathā śaṭhikavātikau|
māṃsajaṃ paṅkadigdhaṃ ca samudronmātham avyayam|| 164.98||
raṇotkaṭaṃ prabhāsaṃ ca śvetamūrdhānam acyutam|
kālakaṇṭhaśarīraṃ ca kuṣmāṇḍaṃ śatrutāpanam|| 164.99||
gomāyuvaktraṃ śyenāsyaṃ bhūtalonmāthanaṃ tathā|
yajñavāhaṃ pravāhaṃ ca kākāsyaṃ kākalocanam|| 164.100||
mañjulaṃ vakranāsaṃ ca mahānāsaṃ gajodaram|
tuhanaṃ ca tuhānaṃ ca citradevam ajaṃ kharam|| 164.101||
madhuraṃ suprasādaṃ ca kirīṭaṃ makuṭotkaṭam|
vasanaṃ madhuvarṇaṃ ca kalaśaṃ kalaśodaram|| 164.102||
revantaṃ manmathakaraṃ sūcīvaktraṃ gajānanam|
śvetavaktraṃ suvaktraṃ ca cāruvaktraṃ ca pāṇḍaram|| 164.103||
kaṇṭhabāhuṃ subāhuṃ ca bakaṃ kokilakaṃ tathā|
acalaṃ kanakākṣaṃ ca balānām agranāyakam|| 164.104||
saṃcāraṃ ca kokamukhaṃ gṛdhrāsyaṃ jambukaṃ tathā|
lomaśaṃ ca jarāsyaṃ ca uṣṭragrīvaṃ kamaṇḍalum|| 164.105||
daṇḍakaṃ dīrghavaktraṃ ca haṃsavaktraṃ mahābalam|
ṭuṇḍukaṃ śatapādaṃ ca śatākṣaṃ cāpapṛṣṭhakam|| 164.106||
śikṣakaṃ cāpavaktraṃ ca śākhavaktraṃ ca kuṇḍakam|
mahāyogān mahāsattvān satataṃ brahmacāriṇaḥ|| 164.107||
apradhṛṣyān mahāvīryān samare ripusūdanān|
nānāśastrapraharaṇān nānārūpān mahaujasaḥ|| 164.108||
nānāvaktraiḥ parivṛtān gaṇaiśca gaṇanāyakān|
gajendracarmavasanān vyāghrakṛṣṇājināmbarān|| 164.109||
raktakeśān hariśmaśrūn muṇḍān digvāsaso 'aparān|
jaṭinaḥ piṅganetrāṃśca bhujaṅgakṛtamekhalān|| 164.110||
pannagāṅgadinaḥ śūrāñchavasadbhogīndrakuṇḍān|
pāvanaiḥ paridigdhāṅgān bhasmabhiścandrapāṇḍuraiḥ|| 164.111||
nṛtyato valgamānāṃśca hāsotphullavilocanān|
gaṇaiḥ parivṛtānanyairbahubhirgaṇanāyakān|| 164.112||
kūrmakukkuṭavaktraiśca śaśagodhāvṛkānanaiḥ|
kharoṣṭrāśvamukhairbhīmairvarāhamahiṣānanaiḥ|| 164.113||
manuṣyameḍhravaktraiśca śvaśṛgālamṛgānanaiḥ|
bhīmairmakaravaktraiśca śiśumārajhaṣānanaiḥ|
mārjāravṛkavaktraiśca dīrghavaktrairavaktrakaiḥ|| 164.114||
lakulolūkacakrāhvaśatapatranibhānanaiḥ|
ākhubabhruviḍālānāṃ tulyāsyai ripudurjayaiḥ|| 164.115||
chāgameṣamukhaiścānyaiḥ śukakāraṇḍavānanaiḥ|
ṛkṣaśārdūlavaktraiśca dvipisiṃhānanaistathā|| 164.116||
bhīmairdviradavaktraiśca tarakṣuvadanaistathā|
garuḍakroṣṭukāsyaiśca kākakokilavaktrakaiḥ|| 164.117||
govānaramukhaiścānyaiḥ śyenagṛdhramukhaistathā|
mahājaṭharapādāṅgaistārakākṣairmahābalaiḥ|| 164.118||
pārāvatamukhaiścānyaiḥ kṛkavākumukhaistathā|
lāvatittirivaktraiśca kṛkalāsamukhairapi|| 164.119||
pītakauśeyavāsobhiścīravalkaladhāribhiḥ|
phaṇīndrānaddhagātraiśca citragonasakaṅkaṇaiḥ|| 164.120||
sthūlodaraiḥ kṛśāṅgaiśca sthūlāṅgaiśca kṛśodaraiḥ|
hrasvagrīvairmahākarṇairnānāvyālavibhūṣaṇaiḥ|| 164.121||
gajendracarmavāsobhiḥ śūraiḥ samaradurjayaiḥ|
skandhavaktrairavaktraiśca pṛṣṭhāsyaiḥ sarvatomukhaiḥ|| 164.122||
nānākṛlibhujairvīrairnānābhujagabhīṣaṇaiḥ|
nānāveṣairmahāyogairnānāsthānanivāsibhiḥ|| 164.123||
nānāvastradharaiścānyairnānāmālyānulepanaiḥ|
nānācarmābarairanyairnānābharaṇadhāribhiḥ|| 164.124||
uṣṇīṣibhirmukuṭibhiḥ kambugrīvaiḥ susaṃsthitaiḥ|
kirīṭibhiḥ pañcaśikhairjaṭāmukuṭadhāribhiḥ|| 164.125||
triśikhairdviśikhaiścāpi tathā saptaśikhairapi|
śikhaṇḍibhirdīrghajaṭairmuṇḍaiḥ kapilamūrdhajaiḥ|| 164.126||
citrākṣakaiścitramukhaiścitrasraganulepanaiḥ|
citrāmbaradharairvīraiḥ satataṃ priyavigrahaiḥ|| 164.127||
kṛṣṇanirmāṃsavaktraiśca dīrghapṛṣṭhaiḥ kṛśodaraiḥ|
sthūlapṛṣṭhairmahāgrīvairlambodaramahodaraiḥ|| 164.128||
mahābhujairmahāvaktrairhrasvagrīvaiḥ kṛśānanaiḥ|
kubjaiśca dīrghajaṅghaiśca hastikarṇaśirodharaiḥ|| 164.129||
dīrghoṣṭhairdīrghajihvaiśca dīrghākṣairdīrghanāsikaiḥ|
mahādaṃṣṭraiḥ sudaṃṣṭraiśca citradaṃṣṭrairmahābalaiḥ|| 164.130||
suvibhaktaśarīraiśca dīptimadbhiḥ svalaṃkṛtaiḥ|
piṅgalākṣairmahākarṇaiḥ śaṅkukarṇairakarṇakaiḥ|| 164.131||
dīrghadaṃṣṭraiḥ pṛthūraskaiḥ sthūloṣṭhairharimūrdhajaiḥ|
nānāpādoṣṭhadaṃṣṭraiśca nānāhastaśirodharaiḥ|| 164.132||
nānācarmabhirācchannairnānāvāsobhirāvṛtaiḥ|
hṛṣṭaiḥ paripatadbhiśca nṛtyadbhiśca mahāravaiḥ|| 164.133||
lambakarṇairmahoraskairnīlakaṇṭhaistrilocanaiḥ|
śukodaranibhaiḥ kaiścit kaiścidañjanasannibhaiḥ|| 164.134||
śvetāṅgairlohitagrīvaiḥ piṅgākṣairbhīmadarśanaiḥ|
kalmāṣapāṇipādaiśca jātīhiṅgulakaprabhaiḥ|| 164.135||
cāmīkarāpīḍanibhaiḥ śvetairlohitarājibhiḥ|
rājāvarttasavarṇaiśca mayūrasadṛśaprabhaiḥ|| 164.136||
pāśodyatakaraiḥ kaiścidvyāttavaktrairmahāravaiḥ|
piṅgākṣairnīlakaṇṭhaiśca mahāparighabāhubhiḥ|| 164.137||
śataghnīśaktihastaiśca gadāmuśalapāṇibhiḥ|
śūlāsipāṇibhiḥ kaiścinmahākāyairmahābalaiḥ|| 164.138||
bhuśuṇḍīprāsahastaiśca vīraiḥ paraśupāṇibhiḥ|
pāśamudgarahastaiśca cakratomarapāṇibhiḥ|| 164.139||
citrāyudhadharairvīrairāvṛṇvadbhirdiśo diśam|
ghaṇṭājālavinaddhāṅgaiḥ kiṃkiṇījāladhāribhiḥ|| 164.140||
vṛtā gaṇairgaṇādhyakṣā mahāsattvairmahābalaiḥ|
upatasthurmahātmānaṃ kārttikeyaṃ yaśasvinam|| 164.141||
mātR̥śca pradadau tasmai kauśikīdehasambhavāḥ|
mahābalā mahāsattvāḥ samareṣvaparājitāḥ|| 164.142||
prabhāvatīṃ viśālākṣīṃ palitāṃ vṛṣanāsikām|
śrīmatīṃ bahulāṃ siṃhīṃ vijayāṃ bahuputrikām|| 164.143||
gopālīṃ suprabhāṃ ṣaṣṭhīṃ bṛhadambālikāṃ kṛśām|
jayāvatīṃ mālatikāṃ dhruvaratnāṃ prabhākarīm|| 164.144||
suprabhāṃ vasudāṃ caiva viśokāṃ nandinīṃ tathā|
vajracūḍāṃ mahācūḍāṃ vajranemiṃ mahāprabhām|| 164.145||
añjanīṃ ca bharatsenāṃ kamalākṣīṃ śaśiprabhām|
śatruñjayāṃ mahānāsāṃ krodhanāṃ śalabhīṃ khaṣīm|| 164.146||
mādhavīṃ śukavaktrāṃ ca kīrtinemim aninditām|
gītapriyāṃ mahāmāyāṃ vāyasīm amṛtāṃ satīm|| 164.147||
sarasvatīṃ bhogavatīṃ subhrūṃ ca kanakāvatīm|
sutāṃ lakṣmīṃ vīryavatīṃ vidyujjihvāṃ mahābalām|| 164.148||
padmāvatīṃ sunakṣatrāṃ kandarāṃ bahuyojanām|
santānikāṃ śivāṃ caiva kamalāṃ maladām api|| 164.149||
sudāmāṃ bahudāmāṃ ca suprabhāṃ ca yaśasvinīm|
nṛttapriyāṃ varārohāṃ sitolūkhalamekhalām|| 164.150||
śataghaṇṭāṃ śatānandāṃ śatanetrāṃ yaśasvinīm|
vapuṣmatīṃ ca śīlāṃ ca bhadrakālīṃ ca bhairavām|| 164.151||
saṃhārikāṃ niṣkuṭikāṃ bhūtāṃ catvaravāsinīm|
sumaṅgalāṃ svastimatīṃ vṛddhikāmāṃ janapriyām|| 164.152||
dhanadāmsupradāṃ caiva bhavadāṃ sukhadām api|
ailīṃ bhelīṃ samelīṃ ca vetālīṃ jananīṃ niśām|| 164.153||
kaṇḍūṃ piṅgalikāṃ caiva devamitrāṃ yaśasvinīm|
lambuṣīṃ sanakāṃ caiva citrasenām athācalām|| 164.154||
kukūnikāṃ śaṅkhinikāṃ tathā jharjharikām api|
kuṇḍālikāṃ lokavilāṃ kaṇḍarāṃ ca śatodarīm|| 164.155||
utkvāthinīṃ jurelāṃ ca mahāvelāṃ ca kaṅkaṇām|
manojavāṃ kaṇṭakinīṃ vighasāṃ pūtanāṃ tathā|| 164.156||
vaiśayāṃ carcikāṃ vāmāṃ krodhanāṃ mukhamaṇḍikām|
maṇḍodarīṃ ca ṭuṇḍāṃ ca koṭarāṃ meghavāsinīm|| 164.157||
subhagāṃ lambinīṃ lambāṃ vāmadhūlīṃ vikatthanām|
ūrdhvaveṇīdharāṃ caiva lalāṭanayanāṃ tathā|| 164.158||
pṛthubarhāṃ mahākāyāṃ madhukumbhāṃ taḍitprabhām|
manthānikām unmanikāṃ jarāyuṃ jarjarānanām|| 164.159||
khyātāṃ dahadahāṃ caiva tathā dhamadhamām api|
khaṭaṃkhaṭāṃ mahāvīryāṃ vṛṣaṇāṃ maṇituṇḍikām|| 164.160||
baddhaveṇīṃ dharādhārāṃ piṅgākṣīṃ lambakarṇikām|
āmodāṃ ca pramodāṃ ca tathā lambapayodharām|| 164.161||
śaśolūkamukhīṃ kṛṣṇāṃ kharajaṅghāṃ mahāravām|
śiśumāramukhīṃ śvetāṃ lohitākṣīṃ vibhīṣaṇām|| 164.162||
jaṭālikāṃ kāmacarīṃ dīrghajihvāṃ ca lolupām|
kanelikāṃ vāsanikāṃ mukuṭāṃ ca mahābalām|| 164.163||
lohitākṣīṃ mahākāyāṃ haripiṇḍīṃ ca durjayām|
paśudāṃ vittadāṃ vīrām aṅgadāṃ ca mahābalām|| 164.164||
payodāṃ gopradāṃ śaṅkhāṃ suniṣaṇṇāṃ tarasvinīm|
pratiṣṭhāṃ supratiṣṭhāṃ ca rocamānāṃ surocanām|| 164.165||
gokarṇīm aśvakarṇīṃ ca aśirāṃ kharikāṃ tathā|
kacakracāṃ megharavāṃ meghamālāṃ virocanām|| 164.166||
etāścānyāśca bahulā mātaro mārutasyadāḥ|
ekākṣarāṃ sugandhāṃ ca kṛṣṇakarṇīṃ ca dāruṇām|| 164.167||
kṣurakarṇīṃ catuṣkarṇīṃ karṇaprāvaraṇāṃ tathā|
catuṣpathaniketāṃ ca gokarṇīṃ mahiṣānanām|| 164.168||
kharakarṇīṃ mahākarṇīṃ bherīsvanamahāsvane|
śaṅkhakumbhaśravāṃ caiva saṃgrāmeṣvaparājitām|| 164.169||
gaṇāṃ ca sugaṇāṃ caiva tathā vātīṃ ca kāmagām|
catuṣpatharavāṃ caiva bhūtinīṃ vanyagocarām|| 164.170||
kārttikeyānuyāyinyo nānārūpāḥ sahasraśaḥ|
dīrghadantyo 'atinakhyaśca dīrghavaktrātibhīṣaṇāḥ|| 164.171||
caturā madhurāścaiva yauvanasthāḥ svalaṃkṛtāḥ|
māhātmyena ca saṃyuktāḥ kāmarūpā mahābalāḥ|| 164.172||
nirmāṃsagātryaḥ śvetāśca jāmbūnadasamaprabhāḥ|
kṛṣṇā jīmūtavarṇāśca dhūmrakeśyo mahābhayāḥ|| 164.173||
asurāṇāṃ mahādaṃṣṭrā dīrghadaṃṣṭrāḥ sitāmbarāḥ|
ūrdhvakarṇīdharāścaiva piṅgākṣyo lambamekhalāḥ|| 164.174||
lambodaryo vilamboṣṭhyo lambakarṇapayodharāḥ|
tāmrākṣyastāmravaktrāśca haryakṣyo harimūrdhajāḥ|| 164.175||
vṛkṣacatvaravāsinyaścatuṣpathaniketanāḥ|
guhāśmaśānavāsinyaḥ śailaprasravaṇālayāḥ|| 164.176||
nānābharaṇadhāriṇyo nānāsraganulepanāḥ|
nānāvastrāṇi bibhratyo nānāyudhadharāstathā|| 164.177||
etāścānyāśca saṃhṛṣṭā dadau skandāya kauśikī|
vaijayantīṃ dadau tasmai mālām añcitakesarām|| 164.178||
viṣṇurvividhagaṇḍāḍhyām utphullāṃ cārudarśanām|
vāsasī virajaske ca taruṇārkasamaprabhe|| 164.179||
samprītā prītamanase dadau skandāya pārvatī|
kamaṇḍaluṃ sudhāvārisampūrṇam amṛtodbhavam|| 164.180||
dadau prītā kumārāya gaṅgā gambhīracetase|
garutmān dayitaṃ putraṃ citrabarhaṃ śikhaṇḍinam|| 164.181||
dadau skandāya samprīto balinaṃ kāmarūpiṇam|
tāmracūḍam adādvīram aruṇaścaraṇāyudham|| 164.182||
bhavavīryajavopetaṃ skandāya priyadarśanam|
mahābhārasahaṃ chāgaṃ kāmagaṃ kāmarūpiṇam|
pradadau varuṇastasmai skandāya balavattaram|| 164.183||
brahmaṇyāya dadau brahmā medhyaṃ kṛṣṇājināmbaram|
pramadāhāvavibhrāntaṃ locanodarasannibham|| 164.184||
tejasāṃ nidhaye tasmai dadau daṇḍaṃ bṛhaspatiḥ|
skandāya paramaprītaścārucāmīkarasrajam|| 164.185||
senāpatiṃ tam abhiṣicya hutāśaputraṃ samyak prahṛṣṭamanaso vibudhāḥ sametāḥ|
daityeśvarasya nidhanāya mahāprabhāvā yātrāṃ surārijayinīsahitāḥ pracakruḥ|| 164.186||
|| iti skandapurāṇe senāpatyābhiṣeke
catuḥṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 164.164||

pañcaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
skandaṃ purodhāya surāḥ samastāḥ sannāhayāmāsuranīkam āśu|
āhatya bherīḥ śataśo mahadbhirdaṇḍairdṛḍhaṃ hāṭakaratnacitraiḥ|| 165.1||
digvāraṇān bhūdharakūṭakalpān mandākinīvāribhirāplutāṅgān|
ānāyya gandhairvividhaiśca mālyairabhyarcayāṃcakruranīkamukhyāḥ|| 165.2||
citrāṇi varmāṇi tato babandhurbaddhvā prayatnātiśayena kakṣe|
teṣāṃ suyatnādgajavājimukhyān haimāni yantrāṇi tathāyudhānām|| 165.3||
citrāḥ samucchiśriyire patākā dhvajāśca cāmīkaracārudaṇḍāḥ|
kṣurapramālā vividhā babandhuḥ pakṣeṣu ghaṇṭāśca samāsasarjuḥ|| 165.4||
rathaṃ ca kārtasvaracārucakraṃ sāṃgrāmikaṃ ratnamarīcicitram|
saṃyojayāmāsurudāraveṣaiḥ prahṛṣṭacittaiḥ khagamaisturaṅgaiḥ|| 165.5||
paryaccham ambhoruhagarbhagauraṃ babandha śakraḥ kavacaṃ mahārham|
vakṣasyabhedye haricandanākte vajraprabhāprajvalitaprakāśam|| 165.6||
babandhuruccairviniyamya piṅgā jaṭā bhujaṅgairbṛhatīḥ śvasadbhiḥ|
citrāṇi hṛṣṭāḥ kavacāni rudrā vakṣaḥsu daityadvipavikṣateṣu|| 165.7||
citraṃ dadhānaḥ kavacaṃ mahādyutirnibaddhanistriṃśatalāṅgulitravān|
bibhraddhanuḥ sajjam apīddhapauruṣo jahau śaśāṅkaḥ sahajāṃ na saumyatām|| 165.8||
yatnādbabandhuḥ kavacāni sūryāḥ kiṃcitpradīptāni tadā svadīptyā|
lauhānyabhedyāni śaraiḥ parāstaiścārūṇi cāmīkaracitritāni|| 165.9||
nibaddhabhāsvatkavacaḥ sudhanvā supīnanistriṃśanibaddhapārśvaḥ|
gṛhītadaṇḍo vinibaddhamaulirbhayānako 'abhūt sutarāṃ yamo 'api|| 165.10||
rucā parītaḥ parayātimātraṃ sphuran muhuḥ pronnatapūrvakāyaḥ|
parābhavaṃ vidviṣatāṃ samāje pracetasaḥ khyāpayatīva pāśaḥ|| 165.11||
dṛṣṭiṃ dhaneśo 'api hutāśapiṅgāṃ dadhadgadāyāṃ parighorubāhuḥ|
īśaprasādena nijena veti suradviṣām āhanane vināśam|| 165.12||
sainye 'atha devadviṣatāṃ nipeturulkāḥ sphuradvahnikaṇā bṛhatyaḥ|
vinā ghanairvyoma rarāsa bhīmaṃ savṛkṣaśailā vicacāla corvī|| 165.13||
rajo nabhastaḥ paritaḥ papāta vāteritaṃ rāsabhapṛṣṭhadhūsram|
dhvajā nipeturdṛḍhahemadaṇḍā raktāmbuvṛṣṭiṃ sasṛjuḥ payodāḥ|| 165.14||
muhurmuhurdainyaparitacitāḥ kaduṣṇam asraṃ mumucustaraṅgāḥ|
kapolabhittīḥ prajahau gajānāṃ madaśca pārāvatakaṇṭhanīlaḥ|| 165.15||
sthāneṣu dīpteṣu vineduruccairdīptasvarāḥ pakṣimṛgāśvasaṃghāḥ|
prasādamālāḥ parito vimudran vavau vivṛddhaḥ paruṣo nabhasvān|| 165.16||
senā prahṛṣṭā mahatī surāṇām abhyāyayau daityapatiṃ rarāṇā|
daityo 'api devāgamanaṃ viditvā sannāhayāmāsa tadā svasainyam|| 165.17||
sainyāni tāni tridaśāsurāṇām anyonyam āsedurudāyudhāni|
kṣubdhānyatīva pralaye mahābdheḥ pūrvāparāṇīva tadā jalāni|| 165.18||
niśāmya daityā raṇatūryanisvanaṃ prarūḍhagarvā balino jayotsukāḥ|
atipraharṣādasamāptamaṅgalā gṛhītaśastrāḥ samarāya niryayuḥ|| 165.19||
rathāśvapādātasamuddhataṃ rajo raṇājire vānarakaṇṭhadhūsaram|
svanaśca teṣām atidāruṇo mahān nabhastadā vyāpa diśaśca sarvataḥ|| 165.20||
samudyatairdānavadevatāyudhairdhvajaiḥ patākātapavāraṇaistathā|
babhau savidyucchaśiśakrakārmukaṃ sahaṃsapaṅktīva tadā nabhastalam|| 165.21||
śastrāṇi gātreṣu tantutravatsu nipātyamānāni parasparasya|
daityāmarairāhanane pracakruḥ śabdaṃ sphuradvahnikiṇaiḥ sametam|| 165.22||
dṛṣṭvāsurān sattvabalopapannān surāḥ sahāyānanapekṣya kecit|
sannehire mattagajānivebhā madāmbubhiḥ śyāmakapoladeśāḥ|| 165.23||
balāni vegādabhisṛtya dūram agresarāṇi tridaśāsurāṇām|
svajīvitāśām apahāya jaghnuranyonyam āviṣkṛtapauruṣāṇi|| 165.24||
nikāmavairāśayamānasānāṃ jighāṃsatāṃ tatra paraspareṇa|
sa samprahārastumulastadāsīt surāsurāṇām anavo mahājau|| 165.25||
sedurgajāstomaraśaktibhinnāsturaṅgamā bāṇahatā nipetuḥ|
saphenam āsyai rudhiraṃ vamanto dṛḍhaprahārānmumuhuśca yodhāḥ|| 165.26||
chināni peturniśitaiḥ kṣurapraiḥ sakuṇḍalāni ānanapaṅkajāni|
anyonyam āviṣkṛtadarparoṣairmahāhave dānavadevamukhaiḥ|| 165.27||
tā mātaraste ca gaṇā vicerurvipothayantaḥ samare 'arisaṃghān|
muṣṭiprahāraistalapārṣṇighātairvikarṣaṇāveṣṭanapīḍanaiśca|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 165.28||
mātaṅgamukhyān dviradaiḥ prabhinnaisturaṅgamān vājibhiruttamāṃśca|
rathān rathaiḥ pattigaṇān padātairgaṇā nijaghnuryudhi dānavānām|| 165.29||
utpatya vegādiṣubhirgaṇendrā gajādhirūḍhān ditijendrayodhān|
muṣṭiprahāraiḥ kuliśograpātairvibhinnamastiṣkavinirgatākṣān|| 165.30||
paraśvadhaiścicchidurāttaroṣāḥ khaḍgaiścakarturbibhiduśca śūlaiḥ|
mahādvipālānanitāntapīnaiḥ prapothayāṃcakrurarīn bhujaiśca|| 165.31||
devyo 'api tān daityagaṇān nijaghnurmahāsamāje samupāttaśastrān|
utpatya vājipravarādhirūḍhān rathasthitān vāraṇadhūrgatāṃśca|| 165.32||
pracukṣubhe tadbalam āsuraṃ tadā gaṇendraniṣpiṣṭabalāgranāyakam|
garutmataḥ pakṣasamīraṇāhataṃ mahāhradaṃ yadvadagādham ambudheḥ|| 165.33||
athābhivīkṣya prasabhaṃ gaṇādhipairnihanyamānāni balāni tārakaḥ|
ruṣā tadā tāmratarāyatekṣaṇaḥ samabhyagānmaulibalābhipālitaḥ|| 165.34||
visphārya śakrāśanitulyanisvanaṃ ratnaprabhāprajvalitaṃ sa kārmukam|
saṃchādayan bāṇatalairnabhastalaṃ marmātigaiḥ kaṅkamayūrapatribhiḥ|| 165.35||
tasyāgamaṃ daityapaterviditvā tadā nanādānalasūnuruccaiḥ|
svapāṇisaṃsthām abhivīkṣya śaktiṃ vicitracāmīkaracārughaṇṭām|| 165.36||
nabho vigāhya pradiśo diśaśca sa kārttikeyasya tadā ninādaḥ|
manāṃsi devadviṣatāṃ prasahya vimohayāmāsa mahāsamāje|| 165.37||
athāpatantaṃ samabhīkṣya tārakaṃ balena guptaṃ mahatā mahāhave|
mumoca śaktiṃ jvalitānalaprabhāṃ vināśanāyāmaravidviṣāṃ guhaḥ|| 165.38||
sā tena muktā jvalanātmajena jvālābhirāvṛtya nabho diśaśca|
anekadhā vyomnyabhavat sughorā māyeva daityān parimohayantī|| 165.39||
papāta vakṣaḥsu ca saṃhateṣu suradviṣāṃ citratanutrabhṛtsu|
samaṃ samastaistvanivāryavegā vidārya corāṃsi viveśa tūrṇam|| 165.40||
devadviṣaste 'abhihatāḥ samastāḥ paryastapṛthvāyataraktanetrāḥ|
saṃdaṣṭajihvādharavihvalāṅgāḥ prāṇāñjahuḥ śoṇitam udvamantaḥ|| 165.41||
tamāṃsi yadvat savitā bhinatti samaṃ mayūkhairatiraskṛtāni|
bibheda tadvaddviṣatāṃ balāni raṇājire śaktibhiragnisūnuḥ|| 165.42||
nihatya devadviṣataḥ samastān raṇājire pronnatadarpavīryān|
prabheva sūryaṃ paritapya lokān punastadā skandam iyāya śaktiḥ|| 165.43||
dititanayasamūhaiḥ sārdham āvipratāpaiḥ (?)
samaraśirasi hatvā tārakaṃ daityarājam|
tridaśasamitimukhyaiḥ stūyamānaḥ prahṛṣṭaiḥ
pratigamadamitaujāḥ śūlapāṇeḥ samīpam|| 165.44||
|| iti skandapurāṇe tārakavadhe
pañcasaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 165.164||

ṣaṭṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan sarvadharmajña mahāyogabalānvita|
śrutam etanmayā kṛtsnaṃ skandasya caritaṃ mahat|| 166.1||
tvattaḥ paramayogeśa guhyaṃ bhagavataḥ param|
tataḥ paraṃ sa deveśastripurārirvṛṣadhvajaḥ|| 166.2||
sampreṣya sahitaṃ devairmahāsenāpatiṃ guham|
saṃnyasya devatāḥ skande kim anyadakarot prabhuḥ|| 166.3||
kva jagāma ca deveśaḥ kim uvācācalātmajā|
kāni cainam umā prāha śaṃsaitat pṛcchato mama|| 166.4||
sūta uvāca|
vyāsenaivaṃ tadā pṛṣṭa ākhyātum upacakrame|
sarvāgamaparārthajño brahmasūnurmahātapāḥ|| 166.5||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
saṃnyasya ṣaṇmukhe devān devadevo bhavastadā|
jagāma sahito devyā mandaraṃ hemakandaram|| 166.6||
sa tasthau āsane tatra haime mahati suprabhe|
nānāratnasamākīrṇe hemaśṛṅga ivocchrite|| 166.7||
tasya pārśve sthitā devī rarāja himavatsutā|
vyabhre viyati pūrṇendo rohiṇīva samīpagā|| 166.8||
sovāca parameśānaṃ praṇamya girijā tadā|
sahadharmacarī yasmāt priyā cāham atīva te|| 166.9||
pūrvapraṇayalabdhā ca tena pṛcchāmyaśaṅkitā|
pāvanāni pavitrāṇi nāmāni tava kāmada|| 166.10||
sārthāni śrotum icchāmi kathitāni tvayā vibho|
evaṃ pṛṣṭastadā gauryā prāha sarvaṃ surādhipaḥ|| 166.11||
sarvayajñaphalaistulyaṃ nāmnām arthaprabodhanam|
mama devi paraṃ guhyaṃ brahmādyā yadvijānate|| 166.12||
tat pravakṣyāmi te devi yena devatvam āpyate|
rujaḥ sarvagato yasmāddrāvayāmi jagatyaham|| 166.13||
rodanaṃ hanmi yasmācca rudrastasmādahaṃ priye|
saṃharāmi jagat kṛtsnam antakāle yato hyaham|| 166.14||
mṛtyuhartā yataścāpi harastena prakīrtitaḥ|
puraṃ śarīram ākhyātaṃ sarveṣāṃ prāṇinām iha|| 166.15||
sarvaprāṇigataṃ yasmāt tat puraṃ śayanaṃ mama|
tasmāt puruṣa ityeva mama nāma maharddhimat|| 166.16||
kadācinnaiva jāto 'ahaṃ na ca me janma yat kvacit|
ajastato 'aham īśāni sarvadaiva prakīrtitaḥ|| 166.17||
abhāvaṃ mayi gatvā tu jagat sthāvarajaṅgamam|
punarbhavati mattaśca bhavastena nirūpitaḥ|| 166.18||
mahatām api devānām aham eva mahān yataḥ|
na ca matto mahānanyo mahādevastato hyaham|| 166.19||
pālayāmi paśūn yasmāt sṛjāmi ca yadṛcchayā|
teṣāṃ ca patirevāhaṃ tasmāt paśupatiḥ smṛtaḥ|| 166.20||
īśa evāham anyeṣāṃ na ca mām īśate pare|
nayāmi ceśatāṃ bhaktān īśānastena kīrtitaḥ|| 166.21||
diśo hi mama vāsāṃsi sarvadikṣu vasāmyaham|
vāsaścāhaṃ diśāṃ yasmāddigvāsāstena saṃsmṛtaḥ|| 166.22||
bhūtānāṃ śaṃkaro yasmāt tenāhaṃ śaṃkaraḥ smṛtaḥ|
lokānāṃ śivakṛdyasmācchivastasmādahaṃ smṛtaḥ|| 166.23||
nīlaṃ yena mamāṅgasya saṃraktaṃ lohitatviṣam|
mīlalohita ityeva tenāhaṃ parikīrtitaḥ|| 166.24||
śūlī śūlena samprokto lakulena ca lākulī|
rudreti kīrtite devi agniṣṭomaphalaṃ smṛtam|| 166.25||
haretyabhihite cāpi gosavasya phalaṃ labhet|
bhaveti kīrtite sadyaḥ sarvapāpairvimucyate|| 166.26||
puruṣeti paraṃ saukhyam ajeti ca salokatām|
īśāneti mahaiśvaryaṃ mahādeveti cākṣayam|| 166.27||
digvāseti paraṃ mokṣaṃ śaṃkareti sukhaṃ mahat|
śiveti śivam atyarthaṃ śūlīti paramaṃ balam|| 166.28||
lākulīti parā/llokān kīrtaya/llabhata naraḥ|
sarvayajñaphalānīha kīrtayan nīlalohitam|| 166.29||
labhate devi madbhakto mayi cāvāsam avyayam|
evaṃ tat kathitaṃ vyāsa nāmnām arthaprabodhanam|| 166.30||
śūlinā devadevena devyāḥ priyahitecchayā|
kim anyat pṛcchasi brahman vada yāvadbravīmi te|| 166.31||
vyāsa uvāca|
śvetajīvaprado rudra iti pūrvaṃ tvayā mune|
proktaṃ paramadharmajña tanme brūhi samāsataḥ|| 166.32||
pradadau katham īśānastajjīvaṃ munaye vibho|
kimarthaṃ kva ca yogeśa kaścāsau śveta ucyate|| 166.33||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vatsa yathā dattaṃ punarjanma pinākinā|
yamena hriyamāṇāya śvetāya vigatāyuṣe|| 166.34||
āsīddarbhadhvajo nāma bṛhaspatisamo muniḥ|
sarvavidyāvinītātmā yasya putraḥ kuśadhvajaḥ|| 166.35||
babhūva sumahātejā viśvāmitra ivāparaḥ|
priyastasyābhavat putraḥ śveto nāma mahādyutiḥ|| 166.36||
tasya janmaprabhṛtyeva kuśadhvajasutasya vai|
chāyevānapagā bhaktirbabhūva vṛṣabhadhvaje|| 166.37||
tiṣṭhato gacchataścāpi svapatastapyatastathā|
sarvabhāvena deveśaṃ dhyāyaṃstasthau mahāmuniḥ|| 166.38||
atha kālena viprendra vipṛthurnāma dānavaḥ|
vavre duhitaraṃ gatvā śvetasya pitaraṃ balī|| 166.39||
na ca tasmai sutāṃ prādāt tām asau suravidviṣe|
sa tena nihato rātrau balāddarbhadhvajo 'api ca|| 166.40||
jāmātā kāṅkṣitaścāsīt tena cakragadādharaḥ|
viṣṇuḥ paramadharmātmā duhitrā cāsya suvrata|| 166.41||
tasya taṃ duhitā jñātvā hataṃ pitaram ātmanaḥ|
jagāma tapase sādhvī parahetormahāvratā || 166.42||
śveto 'api tat tato jñātvā vairāgyaṃ param āsthitaḥ|
narmadātīram āsādya ekacitto jitendriyaḥ|| 166.43||
rudram evārpitāvasthastanniṣṭhastatparāyaṇaḥ|
tapyamānastapo ghoraṃ tasthau yuktastapodhanaḥ|| 166.44||
athāgāt sumahān kālastapyatastasya dhīmataḥ|
āyuryadvihitaṃ dhātrā tat tasya kṣayam abhyagāt|| 166.45||
kṣīṇāyuṣam atho jñātvā śvetaṃ mṛtyuviceṣṭitam|
suto vivasvato hṛṣṭaḥ kālamṛtyupurogamān|| 166.46||
kiṃkarān preṣayāmāsa tam ānetuṃ dvijottamam|
tam athābhyetya te dūtāḥ sthitāḥ śvetajighaṃsayā|| 166.47||
tān dṛṣṭvā sa tadā śveto yamadūtānavasthitān|
hā heti maraṇādbhītastrāsātduḥkhapariplutaḥ|| 166.48||
anvacintayadavyagraḥ paritrāṇāya śaṃkaram|
atha vicintitamātrastu girīndraśikharasthitaḥ|| 166.49||
bhaktānugrahakṛddevaḥ śvetaṃ veda yamārditam|
taṃ tathā duḥkhitaṃ jñātvā bhaktaṃ mṛtyuvaśaṃ gatam|| 166.50||
śaṃkaraḥ prahasan devīm idam āha sureśvaraḥ|
śveto nāma munirdevi madbhaktastapasaidhitaḥ|| 166.51||
kṣīṇāyurabhavanmūḍho mṛtyupāśavimohitaḥ|
vyavasthaiṣā purā sṛṣṭā brahmaṇā lokakartṛṇā|| 166.52||
prāṇinām āyuṣo hāniḥ kālasaṃsthānasaṃkṣaye|
brahmāpi hi sṛja/llokān mūḍho bhavati śailaje|| 166.53||
mṛtyuduḥkhānvitā/llokān yasmāt sṛjati mohitaḥ|
so 'api bhakto mamātyantaṃ brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|| 166.54||
tasya bhaktiviśeṣācca gauravācca girīndraje|
anujñātā mayāpyeṣā sṛṣṭirmṛtusamanvitā|| 166.55||
tathā tu sa munirdeva mayi sarvārpitakriyaḥ|
ekabhaktitayā tasya dṛḍhaṃ prīto 'asmi pārvati|| 166.56||
trātā tasya bhaviṣyāmi jīvayiṣyāmi taṃ munim|
tato bharturvacaḥ śruttvā girijā vākyam abravīt|| 166.57||
evaṃ kuru mahādeva bhaktānugraham īpsitam|
śaraṇaṃ ko bhavedanyastasya bhaktimato muneḥ|| 166.58||
evam uktaḥ sa pārvatyā devadevo vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
nandīśvarapurogāṃstān gaṇeśān gaṇapādhipaḥ|| 166.59||
śaṅkukarṇaṃ ca gaṇapaṃ tathānyāṃśca sahasraśaḥ|
muneḥ śvetasya rakṣārthaṃ preṣayāmāsa śūladhṛk|| 166.60||
mahābalāste gaṇanāyakendrā ājñāṃ gṛhītvā parameśavaktrāt|
tūrṇaṃ yayuḥ śvetamunerupāntaṃ dūtān didhakṣanta ivāntakasya|| 166.61||
te gatvā śvetam aikṣanta yamadūtairathārditam|
mṛgam ekam ivāraṇye vyādhairbahubhirāvṛtam|| 166.62||
grīvāyāṃ kālapāśena hastapāde ca yantritam|
mṛtyunā svayam ākṛṣṭaṃ sravadrudhiracakṣuṣā|| 166.63||
vikṛtāsyairmahādaṃṣṭraiḥ saṃraktaśmaśrumūrdhajaiḥ|
vidyutsadṛśanetraiśca lohadaṇḍograpāṇibhiḥ|
yamadūtairmahāghoraiḥ kṣipyamāṇaṃ samantataḥ|| 166.64||
dṛṣṭvā tathā taṃ munim ārttam uccaiḥ krośantam īśetyasakṛdgaṇendraḥ|
mumoca pāśānmunim āśu tasmāt pāśāt paśūnām iva bandham īśaḥ|| 166.65||
gacchadhvaṃ yamakiṃkarā munim itastyaktvā śarīrairdṛḍhairbhakto hyeṣa surāsureśvaram ajaṃ śambhuṃ jagatkāraṇam|
yaḥ sraṣṭā pavanāgniśakramarutāṃ brahmādibhirvanditastrātā so 'asya vṛṣendraketurajito nainaṃ yamo drakṣyati|| 166.66||
te dṛṣṭvā gaṇapān dūtāḥ kālamṛtyupuraḥsarāḥ|
bhayānmuktvā muniṃ śvetam abruvan dūrataḥ sthitāḥ|| 166.67||
pūrṇaḥ kālo munerasya kṣīṇam āyurgaṇeśvarāḥ|
kim anena vimuñcadhvaṃ nayāmainaṃ yamāntikam|| 166.68||
atha nandīśvaraḥ prāha kruddhastān pradahanniva|
akṣatā gacchata kṣipraṃ kṛpaṇā yamakiṃkarāḥ|| 166.69||
yāvaccaite na kupyanti pramathendrāḥ suroṣaṇāḥ|
mā vaḥ siṃhā ivāraṇye vāraṇān madamohitān|
sakṛdeva samāhatya kariṣyanti gatāyuṣaḥ|| 166.70||
athaivam uktā gaṇanāyakena nandīśvareṇāmitavikrameṇa|
bhītā yayuste pitṛrājadūtā gatvā ca cakruḥ kathayāṃ yamasya|| 166.71||
teṣām upaśrutya tadā vacāṃsi tīvrāṇi nandīśvarabhāṣitāni|
ādityasūnuḥ pracukopa mohāt svayaṃ prayātuṃ ca matiṃ cakāra|| 166.72||
athābhyayāt krodhaviraktanetraḥ sarvairvṛto mṛtyupuraḥsaraistaiḥ|
viniḥśvasan nāga iva pracaṇḍo jagaddidhakṣanniva kṛtsnam ekaḥ|| 166.73||
dṛṣṭvā muniṃ śvetam apetamohaṃ vṛtaṃ gaṇendrairharatulyarūpaiḥ|
muñcadhvam enaṃ tarasetyavocannandīśvarādyān graharājasūnuḥ|| 166.74||
kastvaṃ yama śvetamuniṃ vinetuṃ bhavasya dhanyaḥ pramatheśabhaktam|
saṃrakṣyamāṇaṃ svayam eva mūḍhaṃ gacchākṛtātmanniti nandyuvāca|| 166.75||
atha śrutvā vacastasya nandinaḥ paruṣaṃ mahat|
yamaḥ provāca saṃkruddha idaṃ sarvagaṇādhipam|| 166.76||
gaṇendrā gatajīvo 'ayaṃ viprastiṣṭhati mūḍhavat|
kim anena vimuñcadhvaṃ mā vṛthā khedam āpsyatha|| 166.77||
rakṣito 'api ciraṃ hyeṣa mām eva samupaiṣyati|
kālena paripūrṇena kṣīṇāyuriha kaścana|| 166.78||
tapodharmasamāyukto vidvānapi na jīvati|
yadanena kṛtaṃ karma dharmyaṃ garhitam eva vā|| 166.79||
saṃtyajya tadimaṃ dehaṃ prāpnotu gaṇapādhipāḥ|
mamāyattam idaṃ sarvaṃ bhūtagrāmaparīkṣaṇam|| 166.80||
puṇyapāpīyasornityaṃ karmaṇoḥ pravicāraṇam|
tenārpayata me kṣipraṃ śvetam enaṃ gatāyuṣam|| 166.81||
athavainaṃ gṛhītveha sarva eva gaṇeśvarāḥ|
prayāma śūlino 'abhyāsaṃ niyataṃ sa vimokṣyati|| 166.82||
pitṛrājavacaḥ śrutvā nandīśvarapurogamāḥ|
evam astviti taṃ prāhuryamaṃ krodhavaśaṃ gatam|| 166.83||
tataste sahitāḥ sarve śvetaśca munisattamaḥ|
jagannāthaṃ haraṃ draṣṭum ājagmurvindhyaparvatam|| 166.84||
nyavedayadyathāvṛttaṃ nandī sarvagaṇādhipaḥ|
praṇamya parayā bhaktyā bhavāyāmitatejase|| 166.85||
śrutvā tu bhagavān vākyaṃ nandinā samprabhāṣitam|
prāha vaivasvataṃ sākṣāt snigdhagambhīrayā girā|| 166.86||
śvetasyāsya parā bhaktirmayi pretagaṇādhipa|
ataḥ kṣīṇāyuṣo 'apyasya mṛtyurna prabhaviṣyati|| 166.87||
mahatā tapasā bhaktyā mayi bhāvitacetasaḥ|
matprasādājjito mṛtyuḥ śvetenānena tāpana|| 166.88||
mamādeśāt tvayāpyasya naiva kāryaḥ parābhavaḥ|
kiṃ na vetsi raveḥ putra madbhaktā narapuṅgavāḥ|| 166.89||
na paśyanti tavāvāsaṃ dehabhede 'apyupasthite|
asya bhaktiviśeṣeṇa pareṇa paritoṣitaḥ|| 166.90||
anenaiva śarīreṇa amaratvaṃ dadāmyaham|
iti matvā visaṃdehastvarā gaccha svam ālayam|| 166.91||
iti devavacaḥ śrutvā praṇamya tapanātmajaḥ|
paramārtham avijñāya provācedaṃ pinākinam|| 166.92||
tvayaiva bhagavanneṣā sthitiḥ sṛṣṭā purātanī|
karmaṇyasmin niyukto 'ahaṃ janmamṛtyuvicāraṇe|| 166.93||
adhikāranivṛttau hi śakrasyāpi vṛṣadhvaja|
tvayaiva pavanaḥ sṛṣṭo hyahaṃ caiva sureśvara|| 166.94||
na kenacidayaṃ panthāḥ kālamṛtyukṣayātmakaḥ|
vyabhicīrṇo mahādeva kālātikramadhāraṇāt|| 166.95||
evam etāṃ parāṃ sṛṣṭiṃ vicintya vibudheśvara|
moktum arhasi viprāgryaṃ kāle pūrṇe gatāyuṣam|| 166.96||
evaṃ sthitirabhinnā syādahaṃ ca na vimānitaḥ|
mṛtyuścāntaḥśarīrasthaḥ śvetastadvaram āpsyati|| 166.97||
ityuktaṃ pretarājena śrutvā vākyaṃ vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
dīptāṅgāra ivaikasmāt saṃhāra iva pāvakaḥ|| 166.98||
jagatkṣobha ivākasmādutprekṣyaḥ samapadyata|
nandīśasya tataḥ skandham upāśritya pinākadhṛk|| 166.99||
idaṃ prāha vaco vyāsa taṃ dṛṣṭvā yamam āsthitam|
aho dinakṛtaḥ sūnorasya śāṭhyaprabhāṣitam|| 166.100||
kārkaśyaṃ vacasaḥ paśya pratyuttarasamīritam|
paritrāto mayā śveto yama gaccheti bhāṣitaḥ|| 166.101||
muñca śvetam iti prāha mām eva gatacetanaḥ|
kiṃ nvayaṃ mūḍha eva syāduta pauruṣagarvitaḥ|| 166.102||
gaccheti ko mayājñapte sthātum atra bhavatyalam|
pratyuttaraṃ punaḥ prāha mām eva purataḥ sthitaḥ|| 166.103||
evaṃ sa bhagavānuktvā jagatprabhavakāraṇam|
tiryagdṛṣṭiṃ samādhāya saroṣaṃ yamam aikṣata|| 166.104||
sa tena cakṣuṣā dagdho nipapāta mahītale|
mahāvṛkṣa ivāraṇye mahāvāyusamīritaḥ|
bhasmasāttvaṃ yayau tūrṇaṃ prajahāsa tato bhavaḥ|| 166.105||
śvetaṃ tatastaṃ praṇataṃ muniṃ tu sagadgadaṃ mṛtyubhayādviṣaṇṇam|
pasparśa mūrdhni tripurāsurārirvaco na bhetavyam iti bruvāṇaḥ|| 166.106||
prādādvaraṃ śūladharaśca tasmai mṛtyurna te vipra bhaviṣyatīti|
dadau ca nityaṃ gaṇapatvam eva provāca cainaṃ parituṣṭa īśaḥ|| 166.107||
kruddhaśca yasmādaham arkasūnorasmin girau puṇyatamastato 'ayam|
vatsyāmi cehācalarājamūrdhni krodheśvarastena bhaviṣyatīha|| 166.108||
vindhyapradeśe 'amarasiddhajuṣṭe krodheśvare puṇyagirau pumāṃsaḥ|
tyakṣyanti ye deham apetamohāsteṣāṃ gatiḥ śvetasamā smṛtā me|| 166.109||
drakṣyanti śveteśvaram atra ye ca te cāpi divyā gaṇapā mamaiva|
tavaiva nāmnā ca nadī supuṇyā śvetasya gaṅgeti bhaviṣyatīyam|| 166.110||
santarpaṇānnaikavidhaṃ pitR̥ṇāṃ svarlokadaṃ sthānam atīva yasyām|
ityuktamātre jagadīśvareṇa śveto munirdivyavapurbabhūva|| 166.111||
nandīśacaṇḍeśasamānadharmāḥ praṇamya devaṃ purataḥ sthito 'abhūt|
dṛṣṭvātha sūnuṃ vigatāsum arkaḥ śokābhitaptastvarito javena|| 166.112||
brahmādibhiḥ śakrapuraḥsaraistaiḥ sārdhaṃ jagatkāraṇam ājagāma|
vijñāpayāmāsurathāmarāste ādityasūnupratijīvahetoḥ|| 166.113||
mūḍho yato 'ayaṃ jagadīśvareṇa kṛcchraṃ tatastīvram idaṃ prayātaḥ|
prasīda deveśa kuru prasādaṃ jīvatvayaṃ pretagaṇādhirājaḥ|| 166.114||
yathāpurā caiṣa bhavatvidānīm ārttiṃ hi naśchindhi surāsureśa|
vijñaptim evaṃ tridivālayānāṃ brahmādiśakrārkapuraḥsarāṇām|| 166.115||
śrutvā yamaṃ taṃ karuṇāyamāna uttiṣṭha putreti vibhurbabhāṣe|
divyaṃ tataḥ pūrvavadadrikalpaṃ bibhrat sa dehaṃ graharājasūnuḥ|| 166.116||
protthāya tūrṇaṃ bhagavantam āśu nanāma padbhyāṃ sahasā gṛhītvā||
brahmādayaste ca surendrasaṃghā dṛṣṭvā tatastān praṇatānavocat|| 166.117||
brahmārkaviṣṇujvalanādināthaḥ kartā surāṇāṃ suranātha ekaḥ|
sureśvaraḥ somajaṭārdhamaulirdevāḥ prayāta svaniketanāni|| 166.118||
vijñaptireṣā saphalā kṛtā vo maivaṃ kṛthāstvaṃ punarātmamoham|
preteśvaraṃ ceti vaco 'abhyuvāca jagmustato devagaṇāḥ praṇamya|| 166.119||
pragṛhya sauriṃ pitṛrājam āśu śveto 'api tasthau maraṇādvihīnaḥ|
nandī yathā nirvṛtaduḥkhabhāvastathaiva vipraḥ parameśabhaktaḥ|| 166.120||
iti kathitam idaṃ te śvetamṛtyupraṇāśaṃ himagiritanayāyā bharturīśasya śambhoḥ|
phalam avitathabhakti prāptisampadviśeṣaṃ jagati śaraṇam ekaṃ taṃ śaraṇyaṃ namasye|| 166.121||
iti skandapurāṇe śvetavarapradāne
ṣaṭṣaṣtyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 166.121||

saptaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
yat proktaṃ bhavatā guhyaṃ māhātmyam idam uttamam|
nānyasyaitadbhavenmuktvā jagadārtiharaṃ haram|| 167.1||
puṇyāni āyatanānīha devadevasya śūlinaḥ|
yāni dṛṣṭvā na śocanti janmamṛtyū mahāmune|| 167.2||
tāni me brūhi dharmajña yadyanugrāhyatā mayi|
evaṃ kṛtārtham ātmānaṃ mucye yanmunisattama|| 167.3||
vyāsasya vacanaṃ śrutvā brahmaputro 'abravīdidam|
sādhu vyāsa mahābuddhe bhaktimānasi śaṃkare|| 167.4||
sthānāni śūlino yastvaṃ puṇyāni śrotum icchasi|
kṛtārthastvaṃ mahāyoga muktaḥ saṃsārabandhanaiḥ|| 167.5||
śṛṇu vakṣyāmi te vatsa guhyam etat paraṃ hi me|
sthānānuvarṇanaṃ śambhormṛtyujanmabhayāpaham|| 167.6||
ādityabandhanaṃ nāma kūṭaṃ vindhyagireḥ śubham|
sthāpitaṃ tatra liṅgaṃ tu tapanena mahā prabham|| 167.7||
taddṛṣṭvā manujo vyāsa janma prati na śocati|
hemasomodbhavaṃ nāma kūṭaṃ himagireḥ śubham|| 167.8||
puṇyam āyatanaṃ tatra cyavanenābhinirmitam|
ye tadāyatanaṃ śambhorabhigacchanti mānavāḥ|| 167.9||
na cyavanti punaḥ svargāt pralaye 'api samāgate|
udaye tu girau puṇye siddhasaṃghairniṣevite|| 167.10||
satyo nāma hradaḥ puṇyo hemapadmasamāvṛtaḥ|
yatra te munayaḥ satyāḥ satyānalaraviprabhāḥ|| 167.11||
dhārayanti mahātmāna āśīrbhiḥ sarathaṃ ravim|
puṇyam āyatanaṃ tatra sthāpitaṃ taiḥ pinākinaḥ|| 167.12||
amarairarcitaṃ vyāsa siddhavidyādharairvṛtam|
yaistadāyatanaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ bhavabhaktairviyadgamaiḥ|| 167.13||
te bhavasya priyā bhūtvā bhavanti pramatheśvarāḥ|
uśīravījaḥ śailendrastatrāśramapadaṃ mahat|| 167.14||
āgastyasya tṛṅāṅgasya devadānavapūjitam|
mahānīlamayaṃ liṅgaṃ tasmin vyāsa mahocchrayam|| 167.15||
tasmin āyatane rudraṃ tṛṇāṅgaḥ sa mahānṛṣiḥ|
dakṣiṇāmūrtim āsthāya stauti nityaṃ kapardinam|
divaukasastam abhyarcya bhavanti gaṇapādhipāḥ|| 167.16||
uttareṇa nirāloke ravicandravivarjite|
meruśṛṅge mahotsedhe sauvarṇaṃ sthāpitaṃ mahat|| 167.17||
liṅgaṃ bhagavato vyāsa yatrāste śūladhṛk svayam|
uttānapādaputreṇa bhavabhaktiparātmanā|| 167.18||
nityam abhyarcitaṃ liṅgaṃ dhruveṇāste mahāmune|
devānām apyagamyaṃ taddhruvaṃ muktvā paraṃ varam|| 167.19||
jaigīṣavyeṇa muninā aste parvatarājani|
sthāpitaṃ sumahalliṅgaṃ devadevasya śūlinaḥ|| 167.20||
taddṛṣṭvā mānavo vyāsa rudralokam avāpnuyāt|
mokṣavidyāsvabhijñāśca sāṃkhyayogaviśāradāḥ|| 167.21||
bhavanti manujā dṛṣṭvā talliṅgaṃ paramādbhutam|
nandane devarājena sthāpitaṃ liṅgam uttamam|| 167.22||
tapanīyamayaṃ śubhraṃ devatā yadupāsate|
taddṛṣṭvā devatā liṅgaṃ prāpnuvanti paraṃ padam|| 167.23||
kṣīrode sāgare divyaṃ bālakhilyaiḥ svayaṃ kṛtam|
mahadāyatanaṃ puṇyaṃ siddhakinnarasevitam|| 167.24||
tasmiṃścandraprabhaṃ liṅgaṃ sphāṭikaṃ maṇirañjitam|
bālakhilyāstam abhyarcya jagmurīśasalokatām|| 167.25||
sauvarṇaṃ yakṣarājena sthāpitaṃ gandhamādane|
liṅgaṃ bhagavato divyaṃ yat kubereśanāmakam|| 167.26||
mandārakusumairdivyairhemapadmaiśca bhaktitaḥ|
tam abhyarcya maheśānaṃ kubero nirvṛto 'abhavat|| 167.27||
yaistadāyatanaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ kuberasya surāsuraiḥ|
sarvayajñaphalaṃ tebhyo dadāti vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 167.28||
ebhyaḥ puṇyatamānīha yāni gamyāni mānuṣaiḥ|
śṛṇu tāni mahābuddhe sthānāni śaśimaulinaḥ|| 167.29||
sarvaparvatarājasya śṛṅge himavataḥ śubhe|
mahālayam iti khyātaṃ sthānam ādyaṃ svayambhuvaḥ|| 167.30||
yatra sarvāmarā vyāsa caturvaktrapuraḥsarāḥ|
saṃsiddhā munayaścaiva ye ca yogīśvarā bhuvi|| 167.31||
samabhyarcya haraṃ bhaktyā tadavāptāḥ paraṃ padam|
yatra sākṣānmahādevo nyastavān padam ātmanaḥ|| 167.32||
yaṃ praṇamya narāḥ sarve mucyante sarvakilbiṣaiḥ|
abhigamya tam īśānaṃ mahālayanivāsinam|| 167.33||
dehabhedaṃ samāsādya yatra tatra yathā tathā|
na punarjāyate martyo yātaḥ siddhim anuttamām|| 167.34||
na taṃ paśyantyadharmajñā ye 'api pāpakṛto narāḥ|
mahāgaṇapatistatra dvārasaṃstho mahābalaḥ|| 167.35||
sa teṣāṃ gamanaṃ hanti ye narāḥ pāpakāriṇaḥ|
yogino yate devāśca siddhāśca paramarṣayaḥ|| 167.36||
taṃ praṇamya yayuḥ siddhiṃ puṇyaṃ paśupateḥ padam|
tasya saṃkalpanādeva drakṣyāmīti mahālayam|| 167.37||
karmabhirmucyate janturmahāpātakasaṃjñitaiḥ|
mahālayaṃ mahat kṣetraṃ mokṣasiddhipradaṃ śubham|| 167.38||
kulānyubhayataḥ sapta dṛṣṭvā trāyati mānavaḥ|
tataḥ puṇyatamaṃ vyāsa kedāraṃ nāma nāmataḥ|| 167.39||
paraṃ dhāma vṛṣāṅkasya tasyaivottarataḥ śubham|
svayaṃ kila haro devastasminnacalasattame|| 167.40||
jaṭābhārājjalaṃ puṇyaṃ mumoca -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- dabhavat tatra haramauliviniḥsṛtam|| 167.41||
narāstadamṛtaprakhyaṃ ye pibanti jalaṃ śubham|
te bhavanti gaṇā vyāsa kuṣmāṇā rudravallabhāḥ|| 167.42||
mahārūpā mahātmāno nandino 'apyadhikapriyāḥ|
kedāravāsinaṃ dṛṣṭvā devadevaṃ jagatpatim|| 167.43||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
brahmā śakrastathā viṣṇuḥ somo yakṣagaṇādhipaḥ|| 167.44||
arcayanti sthitaṃ tatra bhaktitaḥ parameśvaram|
kedārasalilaṃ pītaṃ yairnaraiḥ sumahātmabhiḥ|| 167.45||
kathaṃ śocanti te vyāsa prāptaṃ kiṃ nu na taiḥ sukham|
kedāre himavanmahīdhraśikhare yat tapaḥ prasrutaṃ
mūrdhnaḥ somamahendraviṣṇumarutāṃ sraṣṭurvibhoḥ śūlinaḥ|
pātuṃ yanna labhantyadharmarucayaḥ śaivaṃ vinānugrahaṃ
tat pītvā bhavabandhanapratibhayānmuktā bhaveyuḥ prajāḥ|| 167.46||
madhyameśvaram atraiva sthānam ādyam umāpateḥ|
gatvā tam api deveśaṃ gāṇapatyam avāpnuyāt|| 167.47||
tatrāpi svayam eveśaḥ sadā sannihito mune|
abhigamya tam īśānaṃ na śocenmaraṇaṃ prati|| 167.48||
trayāṇām api lokānāṃ pradeśe himavadgireḥ|
eṣa śreṣṭhatamo vyāsa sarvasiddhipradaḥ śubhaḥ|| 167.49||
asyābhigamanādeva sarvayajñaphalaṃ smṛtam|
vipannasya pramādādvā gāṇapatyā gatirvarā|| 167.50||
nātaḥ puṇyatamaṃ kiṃcit sarvalokeṣu vidyate|
trailokye cakravartitvam asmin vā maraṇaṃ girau|| 167.51||
cakravartipadāt tasmādiha mṛtyurviśiṣyate|
yāti sāyujyatāṃ śambhoḥ paramaiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|| 167.52||
girāviha mṛto jantuḥ kiṃ tataḥ paramaṃ padam|
mahaddhimavatastvanyat kūṭaṃ siddhaniṣevitam|| 167.53||
yatra devī tapastepe gauravarṇasamīpsayā|
gaurīśikharam ityeva triṣu lokeṣu viśrutam|| 167.54||
kucakuṇḍa iti khyāte tīrthe yatromayā kṛte|
tadgaurīśikharaṃ puṇyaṃ ye 'abhigacchanti mānavāḥ|| 167.55||
aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya te yānti paramāṃ gatim|
ṛṣabhaṃ śṛṅgam aparaṃ vajrasphaṭikasannibham|| 167.56||
yatra nandī tapastepe varaṃ cāvāpa śaṃkarāt|
ṛṣabhaṃ prāpya tat kūṭaṃ sthānaṃ puṇyam umāpateḥ|| 167.57||
dṛṣṭvā pāpavinirmukto rudralokam avāpnute|
anyaddhimagireḥ kūṭaṃ hemakūṭasamaprabham|| 167.58||
yatra bhastreśvaraṃ nāma rudrasyāyatanaṃ śubham|
rudrastasmin girau devo bhastreśvara iti smṛtaḥ|| 167.59||
taṃ namasya mahādevaṃ kinnaroragacāraṇāḥ|
mṛtyubhītāśca puruṣā janmaduḥkhaistathārditāḥ|| 167.60||
tadāyatanam āsādya krāmān āpuryathepsitān|
taṃ dṛṣṭvā manujo vyāsa rājasūyaphalaṃ labhet|| 167.61||
gaṅgādvāre śubhadvāre mahāpuṇye mahātmanā|
dakṣeṇa sthāpitaṃ liṅgaṃ bhaktihetoḥ kapardinaḥ|| 167.62||
vṛkṣāḥ kanakhalā nāma yatrāsan kanakātmakāḥ|
mānuṣāṇām aśīlatvāt saṃvṛkṇā dāravo babhuḥ|| 167.63||
viśvātmā yatra viśveśaḥ śambhurambikayā saha|
bahurūpeśvaro nāmnā naikaprāṇivarapradaḥ|| 167.64||
mānavā yanna paśyanti janma ceṣa (?) mumukṣavaḥ|
vājimedhaṃ daśaguṇaṃ yaṃ dṛṣṭvā prāpnute naraḥ|| 167.65||
yaṃ devavidyādharasiddhasaṃghā gandharvayakṣoragadānavāśca|
dṛṣṭveśvaraṃ nīlapayodakuṇḍaṃ saṃsārapaṅke na punaḥ patanti|| 167.66||
japyeśvaram iti khyātam anyadāyatanaṃ vibhoḥ|
yatra japyaṃ purā kṛtvā liṅgaṃ sthāpitavān dvijaḥ|| 167.67||
japyeśvaraṃ tam āsādya prāṇāṃstyakṣyanti ye narāḥ|
te janmamaraṇānmuktā vatsyanti śivasadmani|| 167.68||
anyadāyatanaṃ vyāsa śaśibimbārdhamaulinaḥ|
mahābhairava ityeva khyātaṃ jagati yanmune|| 167.69||
yatra śūladharo devaḥ svayam eva vṛṣadhvajaḥ|
cakāra bhairavaṃ rūpaṃ nandyumāgaṇabhīṣaṇam|| 167.70||
yaddṛṣṭvā himavatputrī babhūva bhayavihvalā|
krīḍāhetorbhavo yatra trāsayitvā girīndrajām|| 167.71||
saumyarūpo 'abhavadbhūyaḥ sāntvayāmāsa śailajām|
mahābhairava ityeva tadāyatanam ucyate|| 167.72||
bhairaveśvaram āgamya yaḥ paśyeta pinākinam|
maraṇaṃ janma ca vyāsa nāsau punaravāpnuyāt|| 167.73||
yadevāśramiṇāṃ puṇyaṃ tatheśavratacāriṇām|
tatphalaṃ bhairavaṃ dṛṣṭvā prāpnoti narapuṅgavaḥ|| 167.74||
kumbhakāreśvaraṃ caiva tathaivotkuṭukeśvaram|
chagalaṇḍeśvaraṃ caiva mahābhairavajaṃ sthalam|| 167.75||
dṛṣṭairebhistribhiḥ sthānaistrilokādhipatirbhavet|
rudrakoṭīti cāpyanyacchivāyatanam ucyate|| 167.76||
rudrakoṭītrayaṃ japtyā tatra nandī varottamān|
avāpa śaṃkarādvyāsa gaṇeśatvaṃ tathottamam|| 167.77||
yaistadāyatanaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ te yānti paramāṃ gatim|
devadāruvane cāpi bhavasyāyatanaṃ varam|| 167.78||
devadāruvanaiśchannaṃ saralaiśca sugandhibhiḥ|
sadā saṃsevitaṃ taddhi gandharvoragakinnaraiḥ|| 167.79||
yatra vaikhānasā viprāḥ śivabhaktiparāyaṇāḥ|
bhāskarānalasaṃkāśā nivasanti tapodhanāḥ|| 167.80||
bhikṣāhetorvanaṃ tat tu prāviśat kila śūladhṛk|
sa dṛṣṭastatra deveśo munibhiḥ stabdhamehanaḥ|| 167.81||
īrṣayā munibhirliṅgaṃ tasya devasya tanmahat|
vimūḍhaiḥ pātitaṃ vyāsa devadāruvanāśrame|| 167.82||
tasmin nipatite liṅge liṅgahīnam abhūjjagat|
sthāvaraṃ jaṅgamaṃ caiva babhau sarvaṃ napuṃsakam|| 167.83||
brahmādayastato devāste ca siddhā mumukṣavaḥ|
jñātvā śaṃkarajaṃ sarvaṃ tadapāyaṃ sudāruṇam|| 167.84||
saṃstutya vividhaiḥ stotraiḥ śaṃkaraṃ paryatoṣayan|
tatastadabhavalliṅgaṃ yathāpūrvaṃ pinākinaḥ|| 167.85||
jagataśca tataḥ puṃstvaṃ tatkṣaṇāt samapadyata|
tatra taiḥ sthāpitaṃ liṅgaṃ parameśasya bhaktitaḥ|| 167.86||
taddṛṣṭvā vājimedhānāṃ daśānāṃ prāpnute phalam|
evaṃ dāruvanaṃ puṇyam īśasyāste mahāmune|| 167.87||
abhigamya narāḥ kṣipraṃ mucyante sarvapātakaiḥ|
dadhīcena mahaddivyaṃ puṇyam āyatanaṃ kṛtam|| 167.88||
sthāneśvaram iti khyātaṃ triṣu lokeṣu viśrutam|
naraḥ sthāneśvaraṃ prāpya yastyajedātmanastanum|| 167.89||
yogaiśvaryam anuprāpya svargaloke sa modate|
takṣakena bhujaṅgena dṛḍhabhaktena śaṃkare|| 167.90||
takṣakeśvaram ityevaṃ sthāpitaṃ jāhnavītaṭe|
devadevasya rudrasya yatra sānnidhyam uttamam|| 167.91||
taṃ dṛṣṭvā puruṣo devam aśvamedhaphalaṃ labhet|
agastyena kṛtaṃ cānyat puṇyam āyatanaṃ mahat|| 167.92||
āmrāteśvaram ityeva khyātaṃ jagati suvrata|
dṛṣṭvā paramayā bhaktyā puruṣastaṃ śucivrataḥ|| 167.93||
dehabhedam anuprāpya śarvalokam avāpnuyāt|
girau kālañjare liṅgaṃ dṛṣṭvā sthānam umāpateḥ|| 167.94||
aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya rudralokam avāpnuyāt|
puṣpabhadram iti khyātaṃ vindhyaprasthe drumāvṛtam|| 167.95||
bhavasyāyatanaṃ puṇyaṃ devagandharvasevitam|
yat tadrāvaṇaputreṇa meghanādena rakṣasā|
sthāpitaṃ toṣayānena sarvabhūtapatiṃ bhavam|| 167.96||
yatra mandodarīputraḥ sthāṇunā śaśimaulinā|
māyārathapradānena kṛtaḥ prāptamanorathaḥ|| 167.97||
taddṛṣṭvā tatra gatvā ca praṇamya ca jagatpatim|
puruṣāḥ svargam āyānti divyayogasamanvitāḥ|| 167.98||
andhreṣu āyatanaṃ cānyaccharvasya paramātmanaḥ|
nāmnā citrarathaṃ nāma yogasiddhivarapradam|| 167.99||
tripurasya vadhe yatra ratho devasya dhīmataḥ|
amaraiścitrito vyāsa somādityayamādibhiḥ|| 167.100||
samyagiṣṭe tu yat proktam aśvamedhe phalaṃ budhaiḥ|
taccitraratham āsādya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ|| 167.101||
anyaduktarathaṃ nāma bhavasyāyatanaṃ śubham|
surakinnaragandharvaiḥ sadā saṃsevitaṃ śubham|| 167.102||
tatra śrīparvato nāma parvataḥ śrīniketanaḥ|
siddhāmaraśatākīrṇaṃ siddhikṣetraṃ taduttamam|| 167.103||
śūlino yatra liṅgānāṃ puṇyānāṃ varadāyinām|
sahasraṃ sthāpitaṃ vyāsa śilādena mahātmanā|| 167.104||
ye paśyanti tam īśānaṃ śrīparvatanivāsinam|
janmamṛtyubhayam=teṣāṃ nāsti puṃsāṃ kadācana|| 167.105||
anenaiva śarīreṇa tasmin kṣetre bhavātmake|
yogābhyāsaparā viprāḥ siddhiṃ yānti yathepsitām|| 167.106||
manasāpyabhigacchanti ye narāḥ śrīgiriṃ mune|
na te yānti yamāvāsaṃ mṛtyāvapi samāgate|| 167.107||
tataścottaragokarṇaṃ haraliṅgāṅkitāśramam|
taptaṃ yatra tapastīvraṃ rākṣasaiḥ piśitāśanaiḥ|| 167.108||
rāvaṇādyairmahābhāgairlabdhaśca vara īpsitaḥ|
purā yatra tapaḥ kṛtvā prasādya ca pinākinaṃ || 167.109||
trailokye cakravartitvaṃ rāvaṇaḥ samavāpnuvān|
aśvamedhaṃ daśaguṇaṃ taddṛṣṭvā labhate naraḥ|| 167.110||
mṛtaśca rudrasāyujyaṃ gacchatyatra na saṃśayaḥ|
tato dakṣiṇagokarṇaṃ sthānaṃ puṇyaṃ pinākinaḥ|| 167.111||
spṛkkayā jātayā yatra laṅkāmalayasānuṣu|
arcyate bhagavān devaḥ sarvāmaravareśvaraḥ|| 167.112||
eko rākṣasaśārdūlo yatrādyāpi vibhīṣaṇaḥ|
samabhyarcyāmareśānaṃ bhuṅkte rājyam aśaṅkitaḥ|| 167.113||
mānavā ye 'abhigacchanti gokarṇāyatanāśramam|
daśānām aśvamedhānāṃ prāpnuvanti phalaṃ śubham|| 167.114||
hariścandra iti khyāto girirnaikavinirjharaḥ|
jāmadagnyena rāmeṇa yasmin āyatanaṃ kṛtam|| 167.115||
yatra devāśca siddhāśca yakṣaguhyakakinnarāḥ|
vratino yoginaścaiva nemire vṛṣabhadhvajam|| 167.116||
hariścandragireḥ śṛṅgam ākūṭaṃ yairnirīkṣitam|
na te vasanti martyeṣu devā bhūtvā punarmune|| 167.117||
uttare narmadātīre yojanaikapathāntare|
kārohaṇam iti sthānaṃ trinetrāyatanaṃ mahat|| 167.118||
yatra kākāṃ tapasyantīm āruroha prajāpatiḥ|
āruroha yataḥ kākāṃ tasmin deśe prajāpatiḥ|| 167.119||
tasmāt kārohaṇo nāmnā sa deśaḥ parikīrtitaḥ|
tasmin deśe 'avatīrṇaśca bhagavān vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 167.120||
puṇyo 'asau sarvadeśebhyo deśo yena nibodha tam|
kṣīṇe kṛtayuge vyāsa tretāyugamukhodaye|| 167.121||
tasmin pādaṃ mumocaikaṃ dharmo 'adharmanipīḍitaḥ|
dvitīyaṃ dvāpare prāpta tṛtīyaṃ ca kalau yuge|| 167.122||
caturthenāvatasthe ca yataḥ sa bhagavān rabhuḥ|
evaṃ sa dharmasaṃvāsāddeśaḥ puṇyatamaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 167.123||
bhārabhūtistvasau bhūtvā tasmin deśe pinākadhṛk|
bhārān baddhvā dvijātīnāṃ narmadāyāṃ vicikṣipe|| 167.124||
kāruṇyena mahādevo martyajanmamumukṣayā|
tretāyāṃ diṇḍimuṇḍaśca śirāṃsi vinikṛttavan|| 167.125||
dvāpare cāṣaḍhirbhūtvā nṛttenānugṛhītavān|
evaṃ pratiyugaṃ vyāsa tasmin deśe śivaḥ svayam|| 167.126||
avatīrṇaścānugṛhya brāhmaṇāñchuddhamānasān|
teṣām āyatanāni sma sarveṣām eva suvrata|| 167.127||
yena dṛṣṭāni devasya īśānalokam āpnuyāt|
vartamāne kalau cāpi jñātvā duḥkhārditaṃ jagat|| 167.128||
caturaḥ puruṣān sṛṣṭvā svasmānmukhacatuṣṭayāt|
provāca parameśāno lokānugrahalipsayā|| 167.129||
yūyaṃ yāta mahīṃ sarve dvijā bhūtvā tapasvinaḥ|
mām evaiṣyatha yogīśā nītvā viprān paraṃ padam|| 167.130||
te tathoktvā tato vyāsa sambabhūvuḥ pṛthak pṛthak|
mānuṣeṣu tadā viprā mokṣadharmaparāyaṇāḥ|| 167.131||
ujjayinyāṃ gurujyeṣṭhaḥ kauśiko nāma nāmataḥ|
dvitīyo gārgya ityeva jambūmārge satāpanaḥ|| 167.132|| (?)
tṛtīyaścābhavanmitro mathurāyāṃ mahāmanāḥ|
brahmacārī caturthastu kuruṣveva sugotrajaḥ|| 167.133||
bhagavānapi deveśo hyamareśvarasaṃyutaḥ|
atrivaṃśaprasūtasya nāmnā vai somaśarmaṇaḥ|| 167.134||
rūpaṃ kṛtvā sitāṅgaṃ tu jagāmātrergṛhaṃ śubham|
sa taṃ brahmavidaṃ vipram ātreyaṃ sakulaṃ vibhuḥ|| 167.135||
yogasiddhipradānena anujagrāha śaṃkaraḥ|
anugṛhya tadā vyāsa sakulaṃ dvijasattamam|| 167.136||
jagāmojjayinīṃ devaḥ śmaśānaṃ ca viveśa ha|
sa tatra bhasmanātmānam avaguṇṭhya vṛṣadhvajaḥ|| 167.137||
ulmukaṃ vāmahastena gṛhītvā samupāviśat|
tatra prathamam ādāya śiṣyaṃ kauśikam īśvaraḥ|| 167.138||
jambūmārge dvitīyaṃ ca mathurāyāṃ tato 'aparam|
kānyakubje tataścānyam anugṛhya jagatpatiḥ|| 167.139||
svasiddhāntaṃ dadau yogam uvācedaṃ ca lākulī|
rahasyaṃ paramaṃ hīdaṃ pañcārtha iti saṃjñitam|| 167.140||
viprān mocayituṃ datto yuṣmabhyaṃ martyabandhanāt|
anayā dīkṣayā viprān prāpayadhvaṃ paraṃ padam|| 167.141||
nadītīreṣu medhyeṣu puṇyeṣu āyataneṣu ca|
śūnyāgāreṣvaraṇyeṣu vāso vaḥ saṅgavarjitaḥ|| 167.142||
vaco bhagavataḥ śrutvā śiṣyāḥ paśupateḥ svayam|
yathājñaptam akurvanta sarve te bhavatejasaḥ|| 167.143||
dharmapādāṅkite deśe avatīrṇo yato bhavaḥ|
sa deśaḥ paramastasmānmahāpuṇyatamaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 167.144||
āśramo yogināṃ yatra pravṛttaḥ pāpanāśanaḥ|
aṣṭāyatanam ityevaṃ sthānam atra mahātmanaḥ|| 167.145||
yaddṛṣṭvā manujā vyāsa prāpnuvanti paraṃ padam|
kārohaṇaṃ śivasthānaṃ ye 'abhigacchanti mānavāḥ|| 167.146||
garbhaśayyābhayaṃ teṣāṃ na bhavenmunisattama|
mahīnarmadayormadhyaṃ sahyasya ca yadantaram|| 167.147||
etat paśupateḥ kṣetraṃ purāṇam ṛṣibhiḥ stutam|
tadāgatya naro vyāsa yadyapi syāt supāpakṛt|
sarvapāpavinirmukto yatheṣṭāṃ prāpnuyādgatim|| 167.148||
kārohaṇaṃ sthānam atīva puṇyaṃ śaivāni yatrāyatanāni dhīmat|
gatvā narāstāni mahāphalāni saṃsāragehaṃ na punarviśanti|| 167.149||
puṇyam āyatanaṃ cānyat saptalokābhivanditam|
vārāṇasyā muniśreṣṭha yatra sannihito haraḥ|| 167.150||
tatra bhāgīrathī puṇyā uttarāṃ bhajate diśam|
siddhikṣetraṃ bṛhatkṣetraṃ lokeṣu triṣu viśrutam|| 167.151||
avimuktaṃ smṛtaṃ nāmnā na vimuktaṃ hareṇa tu|
avimukteśvaraṃ dṛṣṭvā devaṃ tatra hyumāpatim|| 167.152||
gāṇapatyā gatiḥ proktā mṛtyukāle mahāmune|
yatrāste gaṇapo dvāri vidyutkeśo mahābalaḥ|| 167.153||
daṇḍapāṇirmahātejāḥ samādeśāt svayambhuvaḥ|
tam adṛṣṭvā na paśyanti devadeveśvaraṃ haram|| 167.154||
yogino 'api mahātmānaḥ puṇyaṃ tasyāpi darśanam|
daṇḍapāṇiṃ śucirdṛṣṭvā haradattavaraṃ gaṇam|| 167.155||
iha loke sukhaṃ prāpya yānti tasya salokatām|
yatra siddhā mahātmāno yogaiśvaryabalānvitāḥ|| 167.156||
channāḥ pradakṣiṇaṃ kṛtvā praṇamanti svayambhuvam|
śakraḥ pitāmaho viṣṇurdhaneśo varuṇo yamaḥ|| 167.157||
hutabhuk pavanaḥ somaḥ svayaṃ caiva divākaraḥ|
tathā saptarṣa.yaḥ siddhā gandharvāḥ pannagāstathā|| 167.158||
avimukteśvaraṃ devam arcayanti yatavratāḥ|
tataḥ puṇyatamaṃ nāsti siddhikṣetram iti śrutiḥ|| 167.159||
yatra jantorvipannasya muktiḥ saṃsārabandhanāt|
prasādājjāyate śambhorguhyam etat paraṃ smṛtam|| 167.160||
gaṅgā dakṣiṇatastasminnuttareṇa varāṇasī|
tat tayormadhyataḥ kṣetram avimuktaṃ pinākinaḥ|| 167.161||
liṅge yat sthāpite śambhoḥ prāpyate phalam anyataḥ|
tat sahasraguṇaṃ proktam avimukte niveśite|| 167.162||
sthāpayedvidhinā yoṣā pumān vā vidhipūrvakam|
sahasraṃ sthāpitaṃ tena liṅgānāṃ bhavati prabhoḥ|| 167.163||
tryakṣaḥ sa gaṇapo bhūtvā rudrasāyujyatāṃ vrajet|
ataḥ kṛtvā muniśreṣṭha brahmādityapurassaraiḥ|
liṅgāni sthāpitāni sma sarvaistatra surottamaiḥ|| 167.164||
tasmin bhagavataḥ kṣetre kāśipuryām anekaśaḥ|
dṛśyante 'adyāpi liṅgāni sthāpitāni mahātmabhiḥ|| 167.165||
smaraṇādavimuktasya pṛthivyante 'api saṃsthitaḥ|
kalmaṣairmucyate janturmṛtaśca labhate sukham|| 167.166||
brāhmaṇāstanna muñcanti vedatattvārthavedinaḥ|
siddhāḥ pāśupatā ye ca bhavabandhamumukṣavaḥ|| 167.167||
prāpya vārāṇasīṃ puṇyāṃ siddhikṣetram anuttamam|
punarniṣkrāntum anyatra kasya jantormatirbhavet|| 167.168||
vedeṣu gīyate vyāsa tat kṣetraṃ śaśimaulinaḥ|
dehinastyajataḥ prāṇān mokṣasiddhigatipradam|| 167.169||
ye 'avimukte vasanti sma narā rudraparāyaṇāḥ|
rudrasya bhavane vyāsa te vasanti na saṃśayaḥ|| 167.170||
tiṣṭhan gacchan svapan bhuñjan karma kurvan hasannapi|
yo 'avimuktaṃ smareddehī tasya janmabhayaṃ kutaḥ|| 167.171||
nāvimuktāt paraṃ kṣetraṃ nāvimuktāt paraṃ padam|
nāvimuktāt paraṃ puṇyaṃ nāvimuktāt parā gatiḥ|| 167.172||
yā gatirdhyāyato nityaṃ pare brahmaṇi līyataḥ|
saiva saṃtyajataḥ prāṇānavimukte smṛtā gatiḥ|| 167.173||
kṣetraṃ puṇyam umāpateḥ suravṛṣairjuṣṭaṃ sadā siddhaye
brahmādyairavimuktam etaditi yat saṃsevitaṃ śāntaye|
ye sevanti tadīśabhaktiparamā martyāḥ śamaprāptaye
muktāste bhavasambhavapratibhayādgacchanti mokṣaṃ param|| 167.174||
prayāge ca tapaḥkṣetre devasyāyatanaṃ mahat|
taddṛṣṭvā manujaḥ samyagiṣṭāṃ gatim avāpnuyāt|| 167.175||
naimiśe devadevasya rudrasyāyatanaṃ mahat|
dṛṣṭvā pāpavinirmuktaḥ svargalokam avāpnuyāt|| 167.176||
dharmakṣetre kurukṣetre sthānaṃ yogeśvaraṃ mahat|
tena dṛṣṭena viprendra gāṇapatyam avāpnuyāt|| 167.177||
rudralokaṃ mṛtaścāsau prāpnuyāt sarvakāmikam|
gāyāyām anyadīśasya sthānaṃ bhagavataḥ śubham|| 167.178||
gṛdhrakūṭeśvaraṃ nāmnā sarvapāpavimocanam|
na taṃ dṛṣṭvā vimuhyanti mṛtyukāle narottamāḥ|| 167.179||
tatra bhasma samālabhya sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
dvādaśābdavratastāpi dvijaḥ phalam avāpnuyāt|| 167.180||
ayandāyatanaṃ puṇyaṃ magadhāsu pinākinaḥ|
nagare pāṭalīputre nāmnā prahasiteśvaram|| 167.181||
vājimedham avāpnoti abhigamya tam īśvaram|
magadhāsu smṛtānyaṣṭau sthānāni śaśimaulinaḥ|| 167.182||
śiṣyaiḥ parivṛto yāni babhrāma nakulīśvaraḥ|
yāni dṛṣṭvā bhavet sadyaḥ pumān pāpavivarjitaḥ|| 167.183||
yavaneṣu smṛtaṃ sthānaṃ puṇyam anyadumāpateḥ|
tripiṣṭapam avāpnoti taṃ dṛṣṭvā mānavaḥ prabhum|| 167.184||
aṅgadeśe paraṃ puṇyaṃ sthānaṃ proktaṃ pinākinaḥ|
hemacūḍeśvaraṃ nāmnā taṃ dṛṣṭvā na vimuhyati|| 167.185||
bhāgīrathyāstato vyāsa sāgarasya ca saṃgame|
brahmaṇā sthāpitaṃ liṅgaṃ puṇyaṃ tatra pinākinaḥ|| 167.186||
tasyābhigamanādeva sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate|
daśānām aśvamedhānāṃ taṃ dṛṣṭvā prāpnute phalam|| 167.187||
prabhāse śūlinaṃ dṛṣṭvā dehabhede gaṇo bhavet|
puṣkare śaṃkaraṃ dṛṣṭvā na śocenmṛtyujanmanī|| 167.188||
mahendre ca nagaśreṣṭhe rudrasyāyanama śubham|
abhigamya naro vidvānaśvamedhaphalaṃ labhet|| 167.189||
mahākāleśvaraṃ devam ujjayinyāṃ mahāvrataḥ|
abhigamyāpnuyādvidvān gaṇatvaṃ tripuradviṣaḥ|| 167.190||
drimacaṇḍeśvaraṃ devaṃ dṛṣṭvā trāyati mānavaḥ|
kulānyubhayataḥ sapta sarvayajñāni cāpnute|| 167.191||
śaṅkukarṇeśvaraṃ dṛṣṭvā na śocenmaraṇaṃ naraḥ|
tathā himagireḥ śṛṅge siddhakinnarasevite|| 167.192||
ḍiṅgeśvaram iti khyātaṃ rudrasyāyatanaṃ mahat|
abhigamya ca dṛṣṭvā ca taṃ devaṃ jagataḥ prabhum|| 167.193||
śivabhaktiparo vyāsa sarvakāmānavāpnuyāt|
mṛtasya ca gatiḥ proktā gāṇapatyaṃ mahātmanaḥ|| 167.194||
suvarṇākṣe paraṃ sthānaṃ devadevasya saṃsmṛtaṃ |
taddṛṣṭvā manujo vyāsa rājasūyaphalaṃ labhet|| 167.195||
saptagodāvare sthānaṃ dṛṣṭvā puṇyaṃ kapardinaḥ|
aśvamedhaphalaṃ prāpya svargaloke vasennaraḥ|| 167.196||
sthānaṃ puṇyatamaṃ cānyacchreṣṭhaṃ jagati kīrtitam|
nāmnā bhadreśvaraṃ khyātaṃ devagandharvasevitam|| 167.197||
taṃ vīkṣya mānavo vyāsa sarvayajñaphalaṃ labhet|
janmaprabhṛti yat kiṃcit kṛtaṃ karmāśubhaṃ mahat|| 167.198||
tatkṣanānnaśyate sarvaṃ dṛṣṭvā bhadreśvaraṃ haram|
yatra tatra mṛtaścāpi gāṇapatyaṃ labhennaraḥ|| 167.199||
dhanyāste mānavā vyāsa rudrabhaktā mahaujasaḥ|
ye prapaśyanti bhadreśaṃ janmamṛtyubhayāpaham|| 167.200||
ekāmre ca vibhoḥ sthānaṃ dṛṣṭvā svargam avāpnuyāt|
virajāyāṃ haraṃ dṛṣṭvā vājimedham avāpnuyāt|| 167.201||
nepāleṣu ca deveśaṃ dṛṣṭvā paśupatiṃ prabhum|
daśāśvamedhān āpnoti rudralokaṃ ca gacchati|| 167.202||
dehabhedaṃ ca samprāpya paśutvādvipramucyate|
anyaddhimagirau sthānaṃ naikatuṅgādhipeśvaram|| 167.203||
dṛṣṭvā tanna punarmartyo jāyate munisattama|
bhaktānāṃ praṇatānāṃ ca sarvakāmapradaṃ smṛtam|| 167.204||
evam etāni puṇyāni rudrasyāyatanāni te|
kathitāni mayā vyāsa yairgatiḥ prāpyate śubhā|| 167.205||
ya etāni paṭhedvipraḥ prayatātmā dine dine|
tasya sāyujyatāṃ devo dadāti vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|| 167.206||
maṅgalyaṃ paramaṃ puṇyaṃ medhyaṃ sarvabhayāpaham|
sthānānāṃ kīrtanaṃ śambhornityaṃ kuryācchucirnaraḥ|| 167.207||
iti girivaraputrīviṣṇugaṅgādharasya
jagati vasatireṣā sarvakāmapradā te|
munivarasutaśiṣṭā pāpasaṃśuddhakartrī
vada kim aparam anyadvyāsa tubhyaṃ vadāni|| 167.208||
|| iti skandapurāṇe śivāyatanavarṇane
saptaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 167.167||

aṣṭaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sūta uvāca|
śrutvā kathām āyatanānubaddhāṃ candrārdhabimbāsthitamaulinastu|
vyāso munistaṃ vacanaṃ babhāṣe brahmātmajaṃ brahmavidaṃ munīndram|| 168.1||
dharmyā supuṇyā bhagavaṃstvayaiṣā guhyā kathā me vidhivat pradiṣṭā|
sthānāni śambhordayitāni ko 'anya evaṃ parijñātum ṛṣiḥ samarthaḥ|| 168.2||
icchāmi vettuṃ tripuraṃ pradagdham ekeṣuṇā divyapinākadhartrā|
yathā purā bhaktavarapradena tanme mune brūhi yathāpravṛttam|| 168.3||
pṛṣṭastathaivaṃ muninā munīndraḥ praśnaṃ yathāvat kathayāṃcakāra|
dagdhaṃ yathā tat tripuraṃ tathā tvaṃ śṛṇuṣva putreti vaco bruvāṇaḥ|| 168.4||
tasmin hate daityavṛṣendrasiṃhe purā hiraṇyākṣasute pravīre|
bhagneṣu daityeṣu sadānaveṣu mayo babhūvādhṛtiduḥkhataptaḥ|| 168.5||
sa viśvakṛddānavarājalakṣmyā ratyeva hīno makaradhvajo 'abhūt|
ādāya daityaṃ sa hi tārakākṣaṃ vidyutprabhaṃ cendrasamaprabhāvam|| 168.6||
tapaścacārogram ahinakarmā daityau ca tāvandhakatulyavīryau|
te śītakāle himaparvatasthā grīṣme ca pañcajvalanābhitaptāḥ|| 168.7||
vyabhre payaḥplāvitabhūmibhāge cerustapaḥ prāvṛṣi ca prayattāḥ|
teṣām agāddivyasamāsahasraṃ tathā sutīvre tapasi sthitānām|| 168.8||
carmāsthiśeṣā jvalanaprabhāvāstapoviśeṣādditiputrasiṃhāḥ|
ādityatejaḥpratimānavīrā babhūvurādityavapuḥprakāśāḥ|| 168.9||
pitāmahastānabhigamya sarvān priyaṃ bahūktvā vacanaṃ babhāṣe|
taptaṃ tapo vo vigatapramohā varaṃ tvidānīṃ vṛṇuteti hṛṣṭāḥ|| 168.10||
taṃ prāñjalirbhūminiviṣṭajānurmayaḥ sureśaṃ praṇato 'abhyuvāca|
avadhyatām apratimaṃ balaṃ ca jñānaṃ ca divyaṃ paramaṃ sukhaṃ ca|| 168.11||
mṛtyuryathā no na bhavecca deva varaṃ prayacchainam abhīpsitaṃ naḥ|
karomyahaṃ yacca sureśa durgaṃ tribhiḥ purairdivyavimānakalpaiḥ|| 168.12||
tanme bhavet sarvasurairagamyaṃ svacchandasaṃsthānagatipracāram|
ityevam ukto danujādhipena brahmā vacastaṃ mayam ābabhāṣe|| 168.13||
dātuṃ na śakyo vara eṣa tubhyaṃ tasmāt paraṃ sāntaram eva cānyam|
tvaṃ putra yācasva tataḥ pradāsye cintā ca te mā danujānyathā bhūt|| 168.14||
tato mayaḥ prāha vaco vimūḍho varo yathā mārgita eva no 'astu|
bravīmi yaccānyadahaṃ sureśa tanme 'arhasi tvaṃ pradadātu mahyam|| 168.15||
pūrṇe sahasre tripuraṃ samānāṃ sameṣyate hyardhanimeṣamātram|
tasmin kṣaṇe yastriṣu saṃgateṣu pureṣu divyeṣu surapravīra|| 168.16||
ekeṣuṇā tat tripuraṃ daheta sa no vināśī tripurasya bhūyāt|
śrutvā tatastadvacanaṃ mayasya brahmā varaṃ taṃ hṛṣitāntarātmā|
prādādabhīṣṭaṃ danujādhipāya dattvā ca tūrṇaṃ svapuraṃ jagāma|| 168.17||
tato mayastat tripuraṃ sasarja jagadvidhāteva purādikalpe|
ayomayaṃ tat prathamaṃ cakāra tato 'aparaṃ rājatam adrikalpam|| 168.18||
t,rtīyam anyat puram āśu haimaṃ sasarja meroriva śṛṅgam uccam|
sṛṣṭaṃ tatastat tripuraṃ mayena svargasya rūpaṃ prajahāra divyam|| 168.19||
dvārairmanojñairvaḍabhīgavākṣairvīthyaṅganairhemamayaiḥ suyuktam|
candrāṃśusaṃsṛṣṭatalaiśca harmyaiḥ śītānilāhlādasukhapraveśaiḥ|| 168.20||
muktāpravālairmaṇikhaṇḍacitrairālambitaiścitrataḍitprakāśaiḥ|
dhvajairvicitraiḥ pavanāvadhūtaiścalatpatākābhiratīva reje|| 168.21||
prāsādapaṅktisthitaratnakhaṇḍairmahāmaṇīndudyutisannikāśaiḥ|
satoraṇābhyucchritaharmyapṛṣṭhairalaṃkṛtaṃ tat tripuraṃ rarāja|| 168.22||
sarvartupuṣpaiḥ phalitairmanojñairvṛtaṃ samantāt tarubhirmahoccaiḥ|
ramyaistathodyānaśatairupetaṃ prabhrāntaṣaṭpādamayūrahaṃsaiḥ|| 168.23||
vāpībhirākrāntavihaṅgamābhiḥ praphullanīlotpalasaṃvṛtābhiḥ|
daityālayaṃ tacchuśubhe tathaiva pranṛttakekāvihagaiḥ sarobhiḥ|| 168.24||
tathā nakhodbhinnapayodharābhirākīrṇaraktāntavilocanābhiḥ|
savrīḍam īṣaccapalekṣitābhiryoṣidbhirākīrṇam atīva reje|| 168.25||
lauhaṃ puraṃ yat tadadhaścakāra tat tārakākṣāya mayaḥ pradattvā|
puraṃ dvitīyaṃ rajatāmayaṃ yadvidyutprabhāyāsurarājabhartre|| 168.26||
haimaṃ tṛtīyaṃ svayam eva divyaṃ jagrāha rājā maya ātmano 'arthe|
adhiṣṭhitaṃ tat tripuraṃ tadābhūt samaṃ tribhistairdanurājasiṃhaiḥ|| 168.27||
te sarvataḥ svaḥ prabhavān vijitya priyāsahāyāḥ saha mitrabhṛtyaiḥ|
sukhāni tasmin vividhānyavāpustrailokyacintām avicintayantaḥ|| 168.28||
te darpamohapratibaddharāgā nyūnānamanyanta balena devān|
matvā ca teṣāṃ prasabhaṃ nipatya nānāvidhāścakruratīva pīḍāḥ|| 168.29||
vanāni vaibhrājapuraḥsarāṇi saṃchinnavīrutkusumāni cakruḥ|
vāpīḥ pracakruḥ kamalairvihīnā jahruśca rambhādipuraḥsarāstāḥ|| 168.30||
saṃtrastagātrīḥ surayoṣitastairanyāśca cakrurmahatīḥ prapīḍāḥ|
teṣām atītaḥ sumahānathaivaṃ prakurvatāṃ devavināśanāni|| 168.31||
tato mayaṃ pratyatha jātakopāḥ saṃgatya sarve tridivaukaseśāḥ|
vṛttaṃ yathā sarvam aśeṣatastannyavedayan āśu pitāmahāya|| 168.32||
tān āha devaḥ kamalāsanasthaḥ sarvān sureśān parisāntvayitvā|
mahābalāste tripurāsurendrā hantuṃ na śakyā hi balādbhavadbhiḥ|| 168.33||
tasmādayaṃ viṣṇurahaṃ ca yuṣmān pragṛhya śambhuṃ śaraṇaṃ prayāma|
gatiḥ sadā naḥ śaśibhṛt sureśāḥ sa tān balāddhaṃsyati śūlapāṇiḥ|| 168.34||
tatheti te 'api praṇipatya devā brahmārkaśakrānilapāvakādyāḥ|
kailāsam āgamya sureśvareśaṃ dṛṣṭvā haraṃ tuṣṭuvurādṛtārthāḥ|| 168.35||
namastrilokeśvaravanditāya priyādharāyāmitavikramāya|
namo 'astu candrārdhajaṭākalāpakāntiprabhoddyotitaśekharāya|| 168.36||
trailokyadevāya namo 'astu nityaṃ pinākacāpāya namastathaiva|
namo 'astu pradīptāsiparaśvadhāya triśūlahastāya namo 'astu nityam|| 168.37||
namo namo nandivarapradāya jagaccharaṇyāya sureśvarāya|
namaḥ sadā bhaktavarapradāya namo 'astu yakṣeśavarapradāya|| 168.38||
sthitāya nityaṃ himavadgirīndre kailāsavāsāya namaḥ sadaiva|
namo vimukteśaniketanāya sthitāya sarvatra ca te namo 'astu|| 168.39||
bhasmāṅgaliptāya kapardine ca namo 'astu nityaṃ vṛṣabhasthitāya|
digvāsase śvetavarapradāya sarvarddhiyuktāya jagadvidhātre|| 168.40||
haryarkaśakrāgnipitāmahānāṃ sraṣṭre namo deva-- -- --rāya|
sūkṣmāya nityaṃ parameśvarāya nityaṃ namaḥ sarvagatāya dhātre|| 168.41||
namaḥ parāyātipare pumāṃse purāya ṣaḍviṃśakasaṃjñitāya|
namo 'astu śarvāya dhanurdharāya sarvāya sarvaprabhavāya nityam|| 168.42||
somānilārkajvalanāmbubhūmivyomātmakāyādisṛje namo 'astu|
pūṣṇo namo dantavināśanāya kamāṅganāśāya namo 'astu nityam|| 168.43||
namaḥ pradhānāya parāya puṃse yogādhigamyāya sadā namo 'astu|
raudrāya saumyāya vapuṣmate ca namo namaḥ sarvajagatsṛje ca|| 168.44||
vidyāsṛje dharmasṛje namo 'astu sraṣṭre namo yajñasurasurāṇām|
namastṛtīyekṣaṇadhāriṇe ca namo namo nīlaśikhaṇḍine ca|| 168.45||
namo 'astu nityaṃ puruṣottamāya śmaśānavāsāya namaḥ sadaiva|
namo 'astu daityāndhakanāśanāya namaḥ sadā mohavināśanāya|| 168.46||
tamovināśāya namo 'astu nityam ajñānanāśāya namo 'astu nityam|
namaḥ sadā mokṣavarapradāya namaḥ sadāyāmṛtasaṃsthitāya|| 168.47||
bhartre namo bhūmidharendraputryāḥ pitre kumārasya namo 'astu nityam|
namo 'astu vitteśavarapradāya namaḥ sadā śukravarapradāya|| 168.48||
brahmātmane brahmasṛje namo 'astu namo namo devasṛje vidhātre|
namo 'astu dakṣāmarayajñahantre namo 'astu caṇḍeśavarapradāya|| 168.49||
yogeśvarāyāmarasaṃstutāya namo 'astu rudrāya parāya dhāmne|
harāya śarvāya śivāya goptre namo 'astu bhīmāya ca śambhave ca|| 168.50||
guṇairvihīnāya guṇotkaṭāya guṇeṣvatītāya guṇāsthitāya|
gītāya sāṃkhye puruṣāya nityaṃ namo 'astu yogopaniṣatsthitāya|| 168.51||
mahāpurāṇāya parāt parāya sthūlāya sūkṣmāya namaḥ sadaiva|
prasādyamānaḥ kuru naḥ prasādaṃ tuṣṭaḥ pareśāna varaṃ prayaccha|
śambhustathaivaṃ stuvatāṃ surāṇāṃ brahmendraviṣṇvarkapuraḥsarāṇām|| 168.52||
prītastayā stotraviśeṣabhaktyā jagāda vākyaṃ paramādbhutārtham|
tuṣṭo 'asmi devā vṛṇutādya śīghraṃ samīhitaṃ vo yadi kiṃcidasti|
dātāsmi sarvaṃ tadaśeṣato 'adya kiṃcinna yuṣmabhyam adeyam asti|| 168.53||
|| iti skandapurāṇe tripuravadhopakrame devatāvarapradānaṃ nāma
aṣṭaṣaṣṭyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 168.168||

ūnasaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
devā ūcuḥ|
brahmadattavarairdeva mayādyairdānavaistribhiḥ|
durgaṃ tat tripuraṃ kṛtvā bādhyamāno baladarpitaiḥ|| 169.1||
hṛtā apsarasaḥ sarvā dhvaṃsitāni vanāni ca|
sarvānsarvān devān nihanmo 'adya śvo hanmeti ca te 'abruvan|| 169.2||
na teṣāṃ nigrahe śakto brahmāpyeṣa pitāmahaḥ|
viṣṇurvāpi mahādeva tena naḥ sumahadbhayam|| 169.3||
tadyathā tripuraṃ naśyet te ca syurnihatā yathā|
tathā kuru suraśreṣṭha varo 'ayaṃ naḥ pradīyatām|| 169.4||
iti vijñāpitaḥ śambhuḥ sarvaistairhi surottamaiḥ|
idam āha mahātejāḥ surān āśvāsayanniva|| 169.5||
śatam aṃśaṃ sureśā vai gṛhītvā mama tejasaḥ|
rudratejomayā bhūtvā dānavān vinihaṃsyatha|| 169.6||
tataste punareveśaṃ prāhurvākyam idaṃ surāḥ|
śaktāḥ sahasram apyaṃśam udvoḍhuṃ na vayaṃ tava|| 169.7||
kā naḥ śaktiḥ sureśāna tejo māheśvaraṃ param|
draṣṭuṃ dhārayituṃ vāpi prasādaṃ kuru naḥ prabho|| 169.8||
na kathaṃcidvayaṃ śaktāstān hantuṃ dānavān balāt|
bhagavan svayam eva tvaṃ tripuraṃ jahi śaṃkara|| 169.9||
tebhyaḥ kila varo datto brahmaṇānena śūladhṛk|
divye varṣasahasre tu sameṣyati puratrayam|| 169.10||
nimeṣārdhaṃ kṣaṇe tasminnetadvastripuraṃ balī|
sakṛdekam iṣuṃ kṣiptvā yaḥ pradhakṣyati dānavān|| 169.11||
bhaviṣyati sa vo mṛtyurnānyathā maraṇaṃ hi vaḥ|
tacca kartuṃ na śaktāḥ smaḥ prasādaṃ tena naḥ kuru|| 169.12||
tataḥ sa bhagavān devaḥ praṇatān vṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|
punarāśvāsayan prāha samudvignān divaukasaḥ|| 169.13||
yadyevaṃ suraśārdūlāstripuraṃ durgamaṃ mahat|
iṣum ekaṃ sakṛt kṣiptvā pradhakṣye nimiṣe kṣaṇe|| 169.14||
brahmaviṣṇupriyārthaṃ hi śakrasyānugrahāya ca|
tripuraṃ ratham āsthāya haṃsyāmi svayam eva tat|| 169.15||
kriyatāṃ sa rathaḥ sajjo yam āruhya divaukasaḥ|
dhakṣyāmi tripuraṃ durgam ākrāntaṃ dānavaistribhiḥ|| 169.16||
yādṛśaśca hi māṃ voḍhuṃ śaktaḥ syāt surapuṅgavāḥ|
balavān himavatkalpaḥ kartavyastādṛśo rathaḥ|| 169.17||
tato devāḥ praṇamyeśaṃ prahṛṣṭamanaso 'abhavan|
rathaṃ ca sahitāḥ sarve kalpayāmāsuruttamam|| 169.18||
tataḥ sa bhagavān brahmā tathā viṣṇuhutāśanau|
sarvadevamayaṃ divyaṃ cakrustaṃ ratham uttamam|| 169.19||
dhātāraṃ bhāskaraṃ śakraṃ pavanaṃ dhanadaṃ yamam|
vasūn rudrāṃstathādityān gandharvānaśvināvapi|| 169.20||
garuḍān parvatān nāgān guhyakān samahodadhīn|
ṛṣīn siddhāṃstathā yakṣān grahāṃ-- -- -- -- -- --|| 169.21||
-- -- -- --$A$ sitaṃ kālaṃ tathā caiva vanaspatīn|
divasāni muhūrtāni kṣaṇān kāṣṭhālavāṃstathā|| 169.22||
ayane ca ṛtūn māsān pakṣān saṃvatsarāṃstathā|
sthāvaraṃ jaṅgamaṃ yacca nakṣatrāṇi tathaiva ca|| 169.23||
aṣṭau devanikāyāṃstān rathe tasminnakalpayan|
kāṃściccakradvaye cakruḥ pratāpa-- -- -- -- --|| 169.24||
-- -- -- ścii ratha cānyān yuyujuḥ surapuṅgavān|
kṛtvāśvāṃścaturo devān rathe tasmin nyayojayan|| 169.25||
saṃvatsaramayaṃ cakraṃ dhanurgirimayaṃ tathā|
jyāṃ caiva dhanuṣascakrurdevadevīṃ jagatsthitim|| 169.26||
te tam evaṃvidhaṃ devā ratham agryam acīkaran|
sarvadevamayaṃ kṛtvā girikalpaṃ rathottamam|| 169.27||
viṣṇuḥ pitāmaho 'agniśca praṇamya parameśvaram|
rathaḥ sajja iti prāhurvināśāya suradviṣām|| 169.28||
tataḥ sa bhagavāñchambhuḥ stūyamānaḥ suraistribhiḥ|
avaikṣata rathaṃ divyaṃ sarvadevamayaṃ kṛtam|| 169.29||
sukṛtaṃ sādhviti procya dhanurjagrāha tanmahat|
tat pragṛhya dhanurdīptaṃ sarvatejomayaṃ param|| 169.30||
adhaścordhvaṃ ca samprekṣya tutoṣa bhuvaneśvaraḥ|
pitāmahaṃ tato vīkṣya provāca vacasāṃ patiḥ|| 169.31||
ratha eṣa dhanuścaitat tvayā brahman sukalpitam|
dagdhavyaṃ tripuraṃ yena tam iṣuṃ śīghram ānaya|| 169.32||
tataḥ provāca taṃ brahmā praṇamya vṛṣabhadhvajam|
ratha eṣa kṛto deva dhanuretacca te mayā|| 169.33||
tam iṣuṃ bhagavāneva tadyogyaṃ kartum arhati|
tataḥ pārśvasthitau dṛṣṭvā śambhurviṣṇuhutāśanau|| 169.34||
dṛṣṭipātena tau devau samāhvayadarindamaḥ|
tau dvāvañjalim ādhāya sureśānam upasthitau|| 169.35||
svayam eva tataścakre śambhurviṣṇuṃ śarottamam|
oṣadhīnāṃ patiṃ somaṃ puṅkhe tasya nyayojayat|| 169.36||
śalyaṃ ca pāvakaṃ cakre brahmāṇaṃ sa tato 'abravīt|
sārathiḥ ko rathe brahmaṃstvayeha parikalpitaḥ|| 169.37||
tam uvāca tato brahmā prāñjalirgataḥ patim|
mahyaṃ dadāsi yadi ājñām aham eva hi sārathiḥ|| 169.38||
prāpsye kim aparaṃ deva sārathyādadhikaṃ tava|
sarvaṃ śobhanam ityuktvā tato devaḥ pinākadhṛk|| 169.39||
haste pragṛhya deveśam āruroha rathottamam|
rudrapāriṣadā ye ca nandīśvarapurogamāḥ|| 169.40||
śaṅkukarṇapurogāśca ye ca caṇḍeśvarādayaḥ|
gaṇeśvarā mahāyogāstryakṣāḥ paṭṭiśapāṇayaḥ|| 169.41||
nanāśastrapraharaṇā nānāyuddhaviśāradāḥ|
nānābharaṇavastrāśca nānāvidyāviśāradāḥ|| 169.42||
vādayantaḥ samaṃ vādyān bherīśaṅkhasvanān bahūn|
ājagmurgaṇamukhyāste sahasrāṇi caturdaśa|| 169.43||
nānāvidhānāṃ puṣpāṇām upariṣṭāt sahasraśaḥ|
nipeturvṛṣṭayo mūrdhni rathasthasya pinākinaḥ|| 169.44||
svayam eva ca vādyāni vineduḥ sarvato diśam|
rathe yuktāśca te sarve devadevasya śūlinaḥ|| 169.45||
aśaktā bhāram udvoḍhuṃ mumuhurdevatā bhṛśam|
tatastān devedeveśo jñātvā mūḍhān divaukasaḥ|| 169.46||
sahanīyaṃ vapuścakre surāste mumuhustataḥ|
athāsminnantare vyāsa nārado bhagavān muniḥ|| 169.47||
jagāma tripuraṃ śīghraṃ viśvakarmadidṛkṣayā|
athāgatam ṛṣiṃ dṛṣṭvā viśvakarmā mayastadā|| 169.48||
sampūjya parayā bhaktyā nanāma munisattamam|
sa dattvā hi āśiṣastasmai vetrāsana upāviśat|| 169.49||
upaviśyāsane tasmin mayam āha mahāmuniḥ|
prasādya daivatai sarvaireṣa devo vṛṣadhvajaḥ|| 169.50||
ānītastripuraṃ hantum atra yat sādhu tat kuru|
rathaṃ devamayaṃ divyaṃ samāruhya jagatpatiḥ|| 169.51||
brahmāṇaṃ sārathiṃ kṛtvā svayam āyāti śaṃkaraḥ|
nāradasya vacaḥ śrutvā sa tadā dānavādhipaḥ|| 169.52||
tārakākṣaṃ samāhūya vidyunmālinam eva ca|
tathānyānasurān bhrātR̥n bāṇanemipuraḥsarān|| 169.53||
nāradena yadākhyātaṃ sarvam aśrāvayat tadā|
tacchrutvā daityarājastu tārakākṣo 'abravīdidam|| 169.54||
na tavāsti samaḥ kaścit trailokye 'asurapuṅgava|
yodhayennirbhayo yastvāṃ cintāṃ tvaṃ maya mā kṛthāḥ|| 169.55||
kim atra cintyate rājan sarve 'avadhyā yadā vayam|
kasya tat tripuraṃ hantuṃ śaktirvidyate dānava|| 169.56||
saṃgatya daivatāḥ sarve yadi yoddhum ihāgatāḥ|
paśya tān nihatānadya mayaivaikena daityapa|| 169.57||
durbalaḥ kurute bhedaṃ dānaṃ sāntvam athāpi vā|
praṇāmaṃ jyāyasaḥ śatrorvayaṃ tu balinaḥ sadā|| 169.58||
durbalasya ripordaṇḍo balinā vijigīṣatā|
kartavyo vikrameṇeti prāha śukrastadā guruḥ|| 169.59||
tadvayaṃ balino daityā hīnāśca tridivaukasaḥ|
hatvā daṇḍena tān sarvān sthāsyāmo nirvṛtāḥ sukham|| 169.60||
tārakākṣavacaḥ śrutvā vidyunmālī vaco 'abravīt|
mamāpyetadatīveṣṭaṃ rājño 'asya vacanaṃ śubham|| 169.61||
na śaktā yoddhum asmābhirdevatā balavarjitāḥ|
te cedyotsyanti saṃmūḍhāḥ prayāsyanti tataḥ kṣayam|| 169.62||
anyonyaṃ tu vayaṃ yuddhādupāyaṃ teṣu yuñjamahe|
yuddhenaiva sadā daityāḥ prāpnuvanti jayaṃ param|| 169.63||
adya hatvā surān sarvān kuru rājyaṃ triviṣṭape|
trailokyaṃ nirvṛto bhuṅkṣva tvam indro bhava viśvakṛt|| 169.64||
saptalokeśvaraṃ tvadya paśyāmastvāṃ purandaram|
hiraṇyakaśipuṃ smṛtvā hiraṇyākṣaṃ ca daityapa|| 169.65||
bhoktārau jagato rājyaṃ tvaṃ prayāhi tayorgatim|
tataḥ śrutvā mayo vyāsa vidyunmālivibhāṣitam|| 169.66||
naitadevam iti prāha kampayannasakṛcchiraḥ|
yastulyaḥ svabale śatrurhīno vā daityapuṅgavāḥ|| 169.67||
bale vā yo bhavejjyāyannekajātivapurdharāḥ|
budhāstasmin prayuñjanti tadupāyacatuṣṭayam|| 169.68||
samā divaukaso 'asmākaṃ balenāsurapuṅgavāḥ|
tairdevaiḥ sārdham asmākaṃ yuktaṃ sāmādiyojanam|| 169.69||
ya eṣa bhagavān īśaḥ sarvabhūteśvareśvaraḥ|
asmākaṃ devatānāṃ ca sraṣṭā hartā ca sa prabhuḥ|| 169.70||
sa hantuṃ svayam āyāti upāyastasya kīdṛśaḥ|
praṇāmaḥ saṃśrayaścaiva guṇopāyau kapardinaḥ|| 169.71||
dvau_imau sādhane tasya prayojyāviti me matiḥ|
yadi kārkaśyam āsthāya yodhayāmaḥ pinākinam|| 169.72||
tasya jihmekṣitenaiva nihatāḥ sma tato 'asurāḥ|
brahmādyāḥ śaraṇaṃ śambhum arditā yānti śāntaye|| 169.73||
yo 'abhiyuktaḥ svayaṃ tena śaraṇaṃ tasya ko bhavet|
yasya sarvam idaṃ daityā brahmādi prathitaṃ jagat|| 169.74||
abhidhyānāt kṣaṇenaiva praṇaśyeta bhavedapi|
yo heturapavargasya kāraṇaṃ jagato 'a yaḥ|| 169.75||
kīdṛśaṃ tena yuddhaṃ no devadevena śambhunā|
kiṃ na vettha śiśuprajñā loṣṭugiryoryadantaram|| 169.76||
bhavanto loṣṭavo bhūtvā girikalpam umāpatim|
īpsadhve mohitā yuddhe kālapāśena yantritāḥ|| 169.77||
ahaṃ bhakto mahādevaṃ jāne tasya balāntaram|
sapraṇāmam upasthāsye na yotsye śambhunā saha|| 169.78||
yadi yūyam api prājñā mama śuśrūṣavo yadi|
mā kṛḍhvaṃ śambhunā yuddhaṃ gacchadhvaṃ śaraṇaṃ śivam|| 169.79||
tam evaṃvādinaṃ śrutvā viśvakarmāṇam ūrjitam|
nārado bhagavān prāha dānavāntakaraṃ vacaḥ|| 169.80||
viśvakarman yat tvayedam uktaṃ vistaraśo 'arthavat|
sarvaṃ yuktam idaṃ kiṃ tu kālo 'ayaṃ nāsya vartate|| 169.81||
bhavatāṃ tat tapaḥ kṣīṇam aiśvaryaṃ bhuktam eva ca|
klībatām api kurvanto yūyaṃ naṃkṣyatha dānavāḥ|| 169.82||
vṛtaḥ sarvāmaraiḥ śambhurvadhārthaṃ bhavatām iha|
praṇatānapyasau yuṣmāṃstatpriyārthaṃ nihaṃsyati|| 169.83||
kathaṃ danusutā bhūtvā rājāno baladarpitāḥ|
bhītā mṛtyuṃ jigīṣadhvaṃ kṛpaṇā iva dānavāḥ|| 169.84||
prāpsyathādhikam aiśvaryaṃ tyakṣyathāsūn raṇe yadi|
vinā yuddhaṃ vipannānām aśubhā vo gatirbhavet|| 169.85||
api cedyadi hanyedhvaṃ devadevena śūlinā|
pramathendrāstato yūyaṃ bhaviṣyatha na saṃśayaḥ|| 169.86||
guṇaṃ sandhigataṃ nāsti yuṣmākaṃ devataiḥ saha|
vigrahe vo matiryuktā sā ca vyaktā vayaṃ ca vaḥ (?)|| 169.87||
śauryeṇa bhavatāṃ prītaḥ kadācidvṛṣabhadhvajaḥ|
bhavedvaraprado daityāḥ śreyān vastena vikramaḥ|| 169.88||
kariṣyāmi ca vo rakṣāṃ śastrāghātaniṣedhanīm|
uttiṣṭhata danoḥ putrā vijayāya yuyutsayā|| 169.89||
nāradasya vacaḥ śrutvā tārakākṣo mahābalaḥ|
vidyunmālī ca daityendrā bāṇādyāśca mahāsurāḥ|| 169.90||
kālapāśārditā mūḍhāḥ kṣīṇapuṇyā gatāyuṣaḥ|
sādhvetacchobhanaṃ proktaṃ nāradeneti te 'abruvan|| 169.91||
mayo 'api tadvaco buddhvā jñātvā nāśam upasthitam|
śobhanaṃ nāradenoktam iti vākyam uvāca ha|| 169.92||
nārado 'api tato hṛṣṭo rakṣāṃ baddhvā tu māyayā|
yuyutsūnasurān kṛtvā yayau śarvarathaṃ prati|| 169.93||
tataste dānavāḥ sarve yuddhāya kṛtaniścayāḥ|
nānāpraharaṇopetā babhūvuryuddhalipsavaḥ|| 169.94||
tarakākṣo balo bāṇo vidyunmālī ca dānavaḥ|
sannahya sahitāḥ sarve rājānastasthuragrataḥ|| 169.95||
avādyanta tataḥ śaṅkhāstūryāṇi ca sahasraśaḥ|
dānavānāṃ bale ghore kātarāṇāṃ bhayaprade|| 169.96||
saratho 'ayam ihāyāti asāvanyaḥ pradṛśyate|
katham āhata ityevaṃ vacāṃsi ūcuḥ parasparam|| 169.97||
vigatabhayaviṣādāstraipurā daityasaṃghāḥ
paśava iva mukhāgneravagacchan samīpam|| 169.98||
|| iti skandapurāṇe tripuravadhe 'asuravarṇane
ūnasaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 169.169||

saptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
athābhyagāt paścimasāgarasya mūrdhni sthitaṃ tat tripuraṃ ratho 'asau|
nānāpatākojjvalacitramaulirhemopalo merurivādrirājaḥ|| 170.1||
te vīkṣya durgaṃ tripuraṃ gaṇeśā nandīśacaṇḍīśamukhāḥ suyattāḥ|
nādaṃ pracakruḥ sahitāḥ pravīrā yuyutsavo dānavarājasiṃhaiḥ|| 170.2||
caṇḍeśvaraścaṇḍavapurmahātmā jvalatpradīptograkuṭhārapāṇiḥ|
vyādāya vaktraṃ purataḥ sthito 'abhūddevasya śambhoḥ pramathendravīraḥ|| 170.3||
dīptaṃ triśūlaṃ parigṛhya nandī tryakṣaḥ pratasthe haratulyavarṣmā|
pārśve sthito 'abhūt sa ca śaṅkukarṇaḥ pragṛhya dīptaṃ muśalaṃ gaṇendraḥ|| 170.4||
bhṛṅgirharātmā sa ca vīrabhadrastathā gaṇendrāḥ śataśaḥ pravīrāḥ|
vajtratriśūlāsibhuśuṇḍihastā yuyutsavastasthurupetaharṣāḥ|| 170.5||
samāgataṃ taṃ ratham īkṣya daityā yuddhāya nirjagmurupetamohāḥ|
te tārakākṣapramukhāḥ suvīrāḥ sannahya nānāyudhadīptahastāḥ|| 170.6||
sārdhaṃ gaṇendraiḥ samaraṃ pracakrurdanoḥ sutāḥ kopavaśaṃ prayātāḥ|
devo 'api candrārdhaniketamauliḥ śaraṃ na cikṣepa puraṃ pradagdhum|| 170.7||
tasthau tathaivāsakṛdātmanā ca paśyan raṇaṃ tadgaṇadaityapānām|
tataḥ sa nandī gaṇapaiḥ pravīrairacīkaradyuddham adīnasattvaiḥ|| 170.8||
vivyādha bhṛṅgiṃ daśabhiḥ pṛṣatkairvidyutprabhuḥ kopaviraktanetraḥ|
bhṛṅgiṃ samāsādya śilīmukhāste nāśaknuvaṃstasya rujaṃ prakartum|| 170.9||
vidyutprabhaṃ bhṛṅgiriṭistato 'asau śūlena dīptena jaghāna pṛṣṭhe|
sa tena śūlena hato jaghūrṇa tyaktvā ca bhṛṅgiṃ prayayau bhayārtaḥ|| 170.10||
bhagnastathāsau ditijādhipeśo bhṛṅgiṃ samutsṛjya gaṇendramukhyam|
vivyādha tīkṣṇairniśitaiḥ pṛṣatkairvināyakaṃ saptabhiraṃsadeśe|| 170.11||
punastriṣaṣṭyā daśabhiśca bhūyo vidyutprabhastaṃ gajarājavaktram|
jaghāna marmasvabhilabdhalakṣyastataścukopāsya vināyakendraḥ|| 170.12||
sa puṣkarāgreṇa gajendrasiṃho grīvāṃ tadā daityapaterviveṣṭya|
utpāṭayāmāsa śiraḥ śarīrāt padmaṃ hradānnāga iva pramattaḥ|| 170.13||
daityasya kṛttaṃ śuśubhe śirastadvindhyācalendrapratimāccharīrāt|
sahaṃsacakrāhvarutopagītāddhradānnavotkhātam ivāśu padmam|| 170.14||
tato 'aparau daityapatī suyattau nemirbalaścāndhakatulyakalpau|
kruddhāvupāgamya hi śaṅkukarṇaṃ śilīmukhairvivyadhaturgaṇendram|| 170.15||
tau śaṅkukarṇaḥ prasabhaṃ nipatya chinnadhvajāśvau virathau cakāra|
anyau samāruhya rathau punastau bhūyaḥ samāgamya gaṇapravīram|| 170.16||
taṃ jaghnaturnaikavidhaiḥ pṛṣatkairvajrābhighātapratimaiḥ sutīkṣṇaiḥ|
kruddhastadā sa prasabhaṃ gaṇendrastau daityarājau suciraṃ nirīkṣya|| 170.17||
dīptena hatvā muśalena vīrau sampreṣayāmāsa puraṃ yamasya|
anye ca daityāstripurādhivāsāḥ kruddhā viniṣkramya gaṇendrasiṃhaiḥ|| 170.18||
nārācacakrāsikuṭhārahastā ghoraṃ mahadyuddham atīva cakruḥ|
daityādhipāste haratulyakalpairgaṇeśvaraiḥ prāptaśivaprasādaiḥ|| 170.19||
hatā babhūvurhi gatāsavastu mṛgā yathā kesaribhirvanānte|
prabhraṣṭanānāyudhavastrahārāśchinnairbhujaiḥ śoṇitam udvahantaḥ|| 170.20||
vajrāhatā -- -- -- -- -- -- -- petuḥ samudre giriśṛṅgakalpāḥ|
śrutvātha daityau balanemisaṃjñau tau śaṅkukarṇena hatau prasahya|| 170.21||
purādviniṣkramya sa tārakākṣaḥ kruddho gaṇendraṃ svayam abhyadhāvat|
taṃ śaṅkukarṇo ditijādhipeśaṃ muñcantam ugraṃ śaravarṣam āśu|| 170.22||
bhallena daityaṃ girisannikāśaṃ jaghāna mūrdhni prasabhaṃ gaṇeśaḥ|
nipatya kiṃcinnihataḥ sa tena bhallena daityādhipatirmumoha|| 170.23||
protthāya tūrṇaṃ sa hi tārakākṣaścikṣepa tasmai gaṇapāya cakram|
kruddhastato 'asāvabhavadgaṇendrastaṃ tārakākṣaṃ sa hi saṅkukarṇaḥ|| 170.24||
nipātya muṣṭyā prajaghāna mūrdhni samāhataḥ so 'api jagāma kṛcchram|
jughūrṇa babhrāma mumoha tasthau papāta tatyāja varāyudhaṃ ca|| 170.25||
mumoca roṣaṃ virarāva tīvraṃ mamāra paścādasuvipramuktaḥ|
dṛṣṭvā vipannaṃ ditijādhipendraṃ pragṛhya daityā bhavanaṃ mayasya|| 170.26||
gatvā nivedyāsurarājabhartre nādān pracakrurvividhairvilāpaiḥ|
tato mayastān rudataḥ sureśān āśvāsayan prāha vacaḥ suresaḥ|| 170.27||
sṛṣṭaṃ mayā vo 'amṛtam etadāste tenainam utthāpayāśu daityāḥ|
tato gṛhītvāmṛtam uttamaṃ taddaityādhipaṃ daityavṛṣāḥ prahṛṣṭāḥ|
cakruḥ sajīvaṃ hi yathā purāṇaṃ mayaṃ praṇemuśca muhuḥ śirobhiḥ|
sa tārakākṣastata āśu bhūyo yuyutsayā yuddhapathaṃ jagāma|| 170.29||
āyāntam ālakṣya pitāmahastaṃ pūrvaṃ mṛtaṃ jīvitam āśu bhūyaḥ|
provāca vākyaṃ sa surāsureśaṃ nivedayan vāmakāreṇa daityam|| 170.30||
hato 'apyayaṃ śaṃkara tārakākṣaḥ kṛto mayenāśu sajīva eva|
tasyāsti devāmṛtam uttamaṃ hi tenāsurāñjīvayate 'asurendraḥ|| 170.31||
doṣo mahāneṣa surendrahetormṛtān mṛtāñjīvayate yadājau|
tato 'amṛtaṃ tanmayasaṃstham āśu pradhyānamātreṇa jahāra śambhuḥ|| 170.32||
pitāmahastaṃ punareva hṛṣṭaḥ pinākinaṃ prāha vacaḥ praṇamya|
dṛṣṭaṃ mayā yuddham idaṃ gaṇānāṃ daityādhipaiḥ sārdham ahīnasattvaiḥ|| 170.33||
divyaṃ sahasraṃ vigataṃ samānāṃ kṣayaṃ na caitat tripuraṃ jagāma|
kṣipasva dīptaṃ tam iṣuṃ sureśa prayāntu nāśaṃ suravidviṣaste|| 170.34||
pūrṇe sahasre tripuraṃ sametya punarviparyastam abhūt sureśa|
kṣiptastvayeṣurna ca devadeva yogena kiṃ vā tava devanātha|| 170.35||
saṃkalpamātrādidam eti nāśaṃ daityādhivāsaṃ tripuraṃ taveśa|
yadi tvahaṃ mānayitavya īśa vimu`nca śīghraṃ tripure śaraṃ tam|| 170.36||
vijñapta evaṃ caturānanena pratīpam ālīḍham anaṅgahantā|
kṛtvā dhanustadbalavadvikṛṣya yuyoja dīptaṃ tam iṣuṃ pināke|| 170.37||
saṃkalpamātreṇa tadā sa tāni purāṇi devaḥ sahitāni trīṇi|
cakre jagatsṛṣṭivināśakartā jagacca niṣpandam abhūt tadāśu|| 170.38||
viṣṇvātmakaṃ pāvakasomapuṅkhaṃ trailokyasaṃhāra iva pradīptam|
cikṣepa devastam iṣuṃ tadograṃ kṣiptvā ca kaṣṭaṃ dhigitīti cāha|| 170.39||
nandī samāgamya tato maheśaṃ provāca vākyaṃ kim iti praṇamya|
nandīśvaraṃ taṃ bhagavānuvāca mayasya bhaktasya śubhaṃ cikīrṣuḥ|| 170.40||
nandīśa bhakto mama viśvakarmā dahet puraṃ tasya yathā na vahniḥ|
tathānalaṃ somaharī ca devau mamājñayā gaccha nivārayasva|| 170.41||
nandī pragṛhyātha sureśvarājñāṃ tūrṇaṃ yayau viśvakṛtaḥ puraṃ tat|
-- -- -- -- -- -- tulyavego jyotiṣmataḥ pūrvataraṃ jagāma|| 170.42||
dṛṣṭvā mayaṃ tatra sa dānaveśaṃ mūrdhnā natāṅgaṃ vṛṣabhadhvajasya|
mṛtyorbhayārtaṃ śaraṇārthinaṃ ca nandī samāśvāsayadīśabhaktam|| 170.43||
bhayaṃ kṛthā mā maya rakṣitastvaṃ bhaktyā bhaveneti vaco 'abhyuvāca|
nandīśvaraṃ dānavarāṭ sa dṛṣṭvā śrutvā priyaṃ tacchivasamprasādam|| 170.44||
yathaiva rudrāya nanāma mūrdhnā cakre praṇāmaṃ sa tathaiva tasya|
athāgnirāgāt tripuraṃ didhakṣan pradīpayitvā sakalaṃ samantāt|| 170.45||
saṃvartavahnipratimo yugānte jagat prasaṃhartum iva pradīptaḥ|
tam āgataṃ viśvakṛto nivāsaṃ viṣṇvinduyuktaṃ jvalanaṃ sa nandī|
dagdhavyam etanna hutāśaneti vaco 'abhyvācāśu vibhorniyogāt|| 170.46||
tataḥ sa vahnistam uvāca devaṃ kasmānna dagdhavyam idaṃ mayeti|
nandī hutāśaṃ sa tato 'abhyuvāca mayo 'atra tiṣṭhatyamareśabhaktaḥ|| 170.47||
taṃ vahnirāhāsurarājam āśu tūrṇaṃ vinirgaccha mayeti vākyam|
haimaṃ gṛhītvā sa maheśaliṅgaṃ purādviniṣkramya mayo 'asurendraḥ|| 170.48||
pātālam āśu praviveśa hṛṣṭaḥ kurvan namaskāram umāpriyasya|
nandīśvaraḥ so 'api sureśapārśvam āgamya cākhyāya ca saṃsthito 'abhūt|| 170.49||
tataḥ pradīptaṃ tripuraṃ babhūva viśkiṣṭayantrārgalanaṣṭaveśma|
naikāsurāmuktamahogranādaṃ vitrastadaityendravadhūjanāḍhyam|| 170.50||
vātāyane harmyavimānasaṃsthāścandrānanāḥ pīnapayodharāḍhyāḥ|
paryaṅkasuptā madavihvalākṣyo mārgaṃ priyāṇāṃ muhurīhṣamāṇāḥ|| 170.51||
vilocanaistāmranibhāṅgarāgaiḥ śyāmāvadātā jaghanairviśālaiḥ|
daityāṅganāḥ svaṃ dadṛśuḥ pradīptam āliṅgyamānāḥ śarapāvakena|| 170.52||
prāsādasaṃsthāḥ prayayurbhayārttāstrāsena kinnarya ivācalasthāḥ|
priyānathodvīkṣya samāgatāṃstān mohaṃ samāliṅgya bhṛśaṃ vijagmuḥ|| 170.53||
priyā gṛhītvā ditijāstataste pranaṣṭakāmāstarasābhijagmuḥ|
niṣkrāntamātrāḥ śivaśaktimūḍhāḥ petuḥ samudre balaviprayuktāḥ|| 170.54||
daityān samudre patitāṃstatastān matsyā mahānto girisannikāśāḥ|
tīvrāśca nakrā makarāśca ghorāḥ saṃjagrasurnaṣṭabalān vimūḍhān|| 170.55||
jalecarendrāstvapare mahāntaḥ saṃchinnahārāḥ patitāḥ striyastāḥ|
hīnāḥ priyairbhakṣayituṃ pravṛttāḥ karāladaṃṣṭrā vivṛtānanāśca|| 170.56||
tā bhakṣyamāṇāḥ patitāstaruṇyaḥ priyān saroṣaṃ bahuśo nirīkṣya|
rujā mahatyā parikhidyamānāḥ saṃcukruśurdīnataraṃ yuvatyaḥ|| 170.57||
tāsāṃ tadā daityavilāsinīnāṃ reje bhṛśaṃ krodhanirīkṣitaṃ tat|
ratāvasāne parikheditānāṃ priyairivānyām abhigantukāmaiḥ|| 170.58||
sarve tato daityavṛṣāḥ sabhāryāḥ pradahyamānāstripurānalena|
magnāḥ samudre makarairvibhinnā gatāsavo mṛtyuvaśaṃ prajagmuḥ|| 170.59||
śaraśca so 'agnīndujanārdanātmā pradahya kṛtsnaṃ tripuraṃ puraṃ tat|
kṣiptvā samudre sma śamaṃ prayātaṃ śaśāma śambhośca karaṃ jagāma|| 170.60||
daityairhataistaistripure ca dagdhe devān rathasthān punareva devaḥ|
pūrvaṃ yathā divyaśarīrayuktāṃścakāra sṛṣṭipralayādihetuḥ|| 170.61||
brahmādayaste tridivaukaseśā nemurvacaścedam athocurīśam|
kṛtaṃ tvayedaṃ bhagavannaśakyaṃ śubhaṃ mahadraudrataraṃ ca karma|| 170.62||
daityā hatāstat tripuraṃ pradagdhaṃ śāntiḥ kṛtā naḥ sma surāsureśa|
namo 'astu sarvatra sadā sthitāya sraṣṭre surāṇāṃ parameśa tubhyam|
nityaṃ naviñātagamakriyāya namo namaḥ sarvagatāya tubhyam|| 170.63||
tān āha devaḥ sa tadā surendrān brahmārkaviṣṇvindradhaneśvarādyān|
sadaiva yūyaṃ pratipālanīyā rakṣyāśca devāḥ sutavanmayaiva|| 170.64||
pūrṇābhilāṣā hatavidviṣaśca prayāta hṛṣṭāḥ svaniveśanāni|
devāstato devavaraṃ praṇamya jagmuḥ svakīyāni niveśanāni|| 170.65||
devo 'api siddhairabhivandyamānaḥ kailāsaśṛṅgaṃ sahito gaṇendraiḥ|
caṇḍeśanandīśvaravīrabhadrairjagāma kartā jagatastrinetraḥ|| 170.66||
iti kathitam asahyaṃ devadevasya karma tripuradahanasaṃjñaṃ vyāsa tubhyaṃ mayaitat|
manuja idam adhīte yaḥ śuciḥ śarvabhaktaḥ sa bhavati gatapāpaḥ svargabhāgdevajanmā|| 170.67||
|| iti skandapurāṇe tripuravadhe
saptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 170.170||

ekasaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
śrutaṃ mayaitadbhagavan dahanaṃ tripurasya tu|
vicitrārthaṃ yathāvṛttaṃ ka evam abhidhāsyati|| 171.1||
kasmāt kruddho nagendraṃ taṃ krauñcaṃ dāritavān guhaḥ|
pakṣān sarvagirīndrāṇāṃ kasmācciccheda vāsavaḥ|| 171.2||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vyāsa mahābuddhe yanmāṃ tvaṃ paripṛcchasi|
kumāreṇa yathā bhinno mainākiḥ krauñcaparvataḥ|| 171.3||
girirājam athābhyetya meruṃ sarvasurālayam|
apaśyadvāsavaḥ skandaṃ saṃghātaṃ tejasām iva|| 171.4||
śarastambavane dṛṣṭvā kumāram analaprabham|
surarājyamadāviṣṭaḥ śakraḥ papraccha ṣaṇmukham|| 171.5||
kastvaṃ divyavapurbāla meruparvatam āśritaḥ|
na māṃ pūjayase dṛṣṭvā devarājam ihāgatam|| 171.6||
tam evaṃvādinaṃ śakraṃ prāha śūladharātmajaḥ|
brahmādyā māṃ vijānanti siddhā vedavidaśca ye|| 171.7||
tapasā labdharājyena na cirādastam eṣyatā|
kiṃ tvayā jānatā śakra kāryaṃ kiṃ pūjitena vā|| 171.8||
athovāca punaḥ śakrastadevam analātmajam|
mattaḥ parataro nāsti muktvā śarvapitāmahau|| 171.9||
katham evam avocastvaṃ vibudhādhipam āgatam|
yadi mattastvam ātmānaṃ mahāntaṃ manase 'anagha|| 171.10||
mainākatanayo hyeṣa krauñcaḥ siddhaniṣevitaḥ|
suvistīrṇo mahāśailo naikanirjharanisravaḥ|| 171.11||
ehyehi tvaṃ mayā sārdhaṃ kuru śīghraṃ pradakṣiṇam|
ya enam āvayorekaḥ pūrvam eva kramiṣyati|| 171.12||
prabhāvāt tejasā caiva sa mahān nau bhaviṣyati|
bāḍham ityevam uktvātha kumāraḥ ṣaṇmukhastadā|| 171.13||
śakreṇa saha saṃgatya mayūravaram āsthitaḥ|
mahendrasyāgrato gacchaṃścakre krauñcaṃ pradakṣiṇam|| 171.14||
atha buddhvā mahendrastu nyūnam ātmānam ānalāt|
kumāram abhisandhitsurmanasaiva pradakṣiṇam|| 171.15||
kṛtvā sunirvṛtastasthau upaviṣṭaḥ śilātale|
javenātha kumārastaṃ krauñcaṃ kṛtvā pradakṣiṇam|| 171.16||
provācendraṃ tadā dṛṣṭvā jetāham iti satvaraḥ|
aham eva hi jeteti śakrastam avadadguham|| 171.17||
asakṛdbruvata evaṃ tayoḥ śakrakumārayoḥ|
krauñco 'abhyetya vacaḥ prāha kim etaditi bhūcaraḥ|| 171.18||
tataḥ śakra uvācedaṃ kumāraṃ vacanaṃ tadā|
eṣa evāvayoḥ krañco jayasākṣī mahābalaḥ|| 171.19||
nānṛtaṃ vakṣyati hyeṣa pautro himagirervaraḥ|
pṛcchyatāṃ śakra ko doṣa iti āha jvalanātmajaḥ|| 171.20||
taṃ śakraṃ sādaraṃ prāha kena tvam acalāgrataḥ|
kṛtapradakṣiṇo brūhi pramāṇaṃ hi tvam āvayoḥ|| 171.21||
tataḥ krauñco vimūḍhātmā saṃcintya suciraṃ nagaḥ|
ayaṃ śacīpatiścakre mām ihāgre pradakṣiṇam|| 171.22||
-- -- rya prahasan devānityuvāca nagādhipaḥ|
athaivaṃ bruvatastasya satyahīnaṃ tadā gireḥ|| 171.23||
papāta śikharaṃ tūrṇaṃ kuliśena yathā hatam|
tatrāsan yāni bhūtāni surādyāni girīśvare|
tāni saṃtyajya śīghraṃ taṃ prayayuḥ sarvato diśam|| 171.24||
jahṛṣe vāsavaścāpi manasā pūjayan girim|
tataścukrodha rudrātmā gireḥ krauñcasya ṣaṇmukhaḥ|| 171.25||
-- -- -- -- guhaṃ draṣṭuṃ saṃkruddhaṃ vāsavastadā|
ekasthe tejasī pūrṇe vahnibhāskarayoriva|| (?) 26||
atha śaktiṃ samutkṣipya yamānalasamaprabhām|
cikṣepa bhagavān skandaḥ kruddhaḥ krauñcajighāṃsaya|| 171.27||
sā papāta girermūrdhni śaktiḥ krauñcasya satvaram|
kṣīṇāyuṣo yathā puṃso mṛtyupāśa-- -- -- --|| 171.28||
sa tayā bhinnamarmā tu śaktyā krauñco nagottamaḥ|
sarvataśchinnasarvāṅgaḥ sravadrudhiranirjharaḥ|| 171.29||
mūrtimānapatadbhūmau saṃjñāprāṇavivarjitaḥ|
patiṃ vinihataṃ dṛṣṭvā patnyastasya suduḥkhitāḥ|| 171.30||
vilapantyastadā dīnaṃ petuḥ krauñcācalopari|
merurhimācalo vindhyaḥ kailāso gandhamādanaḥ|| 171.31||
pāriyātraśca sahyaśca niṣadhodayavāmanāḥ|
krauñcasya janakaścāpi mainākaḥ parvatottamaḥ|| 171.32||
sarve parvatarājāna ājagmuḥ śokapīḍitāḥ|
parivārya giriṃ krauñcaṃ rurudurduḥkhitā bhṛśam|| 171.33||
bhrātṛputraṃ hataṃ jñātvā devadevī girīndrajā|
śarveṇa sahitā krauñcam ājagāma mahāvratā|| 171.34||
kumāreṇa hataṃ dṛṣṭvā krauñcaṃ bāndhavam ātmanaḥ|
pīḍitābhūt tadā devī dṛṣṭvā pitaram arditam|| 171.35||
himavantaṃ mahāśailaṃ vadhāt pautrasya duḥkhitam|
śuśoca girijā dṛṣṭvā muhurvīkṣya sureśvaram|| 171.36||
bhagavantam athāyātaṃ devyā saha pinākinam|
śokenāpi susantaptā namaścakrurmahābalāḥ|| 171.37||
atha praṇamya deveśaṃ himavānacalottamaḥ|
vyajñāpayata dīnātmā duḥkhaśokapariplutaḥ|| 171.38||
śakreṇānena bhagavan ātmānaṃ bahumanyatā|
nidhanaṃ nāyitaḥ pautro mamāyaṃ krauñcaparvataḥ|| 171.39||
spardhā kāsya kumāreṇa tava deva sutena hi|
nāntaraṃ veda yo darpāt kumārasyātmanaśca ha|| 171.40||
spardhāṃ kṛtvā kumāreṇa hate pautre mamādhunā|
nirvṛto gatadarpo 'ayaṃ sukhaṃ tiṣṭhatu vāsavaḥ|| 171.41||
hate pautre mahādeva nimagnaḥ śokasāgare|
na jīvitum ahaṃ śakto yāsye pautragatiṃ tvaham|| 171.42||
evaṃ vilapatastasya meruvindhyapurogamāḥ|
vinedurduḥkhasaṃtaptā bāndhavābhāvapīḍitāḥ|| 171.43||
pitaraṃ duḥkhitaṃ dṛṣṭvā tathānyān bāndhavān girīn|
abhavacchokasaṃtaptā girijāpi jagaddharā|| 171.44||
atha tān duḥkhitān dṛṣṭvā sarvān govṛṣavāhanaḥ|
mā kārṣṭa śokam ityuktvā tanayaṃ prāha ṣaṇmukham|| 171.45||
mahāntastvadvidhāḥ putra sāparādhe 'api bāndhave|
nāśubhaṃ kurvate kasmāt krauñcaṃ nihatavānasi|| 171.46||
bhrātṛsūnurbhavanmātureṣa krauñco mahāgiriḥ|
kathaṃ bhrātaram enaṃ svaṃ hatavānasi ṣaṇmukha|| 171.47||
sadṛśaṃ karma naitat te manmayasya sutasya te|
brūhi vā sāmprataṃ karma kim atra bahu manyase|| 171.48||
tam evaṃvādinaṃ devaṃ ṣaṇmukhaḥ pitaraṃ tadā|
idaṃ provāca savrīḍaṃ vacanaṃ paramādbhutam|| 171.49||
śakrasyāpanayāddeva krauñca eṣa hato mayā|
asanmantritavān yasmādvijñaptim aparāṃ śṛṇu|| 171.50||
tvatprasādādahaṃ krauñcaṃ jīvayāmi nagottamam|
duṣkaraṃ na hi me kiṃcit tava deva sutasya hi|| 171.51||
uttiṣṭheti tataḥ krauñcaṃ bhrātaraṃ prāha ṣaṇmukhaḥ|
sa bibhrat pūrvavaddehaṃ krauñco nagapatiḥ kṣaṇāt|| 171.52||
uttasthau nīrujo vyāsa āścaryaṃ tadabhūt tadā|
jīvitenācalenaivaṃ ṣaṇmukho vahnisaprabhaḥ|| 171.53||
smaran rudrāddhikṣepaṃ kopasaṃraktalocanaḥ|
samakṣaṃ sarvadevānāṃ śakrasya ca mahābalaḥ|| 171.54||
vāyuviṣṇuyamānāṃ ca brahmaṇaśca mahātmanaḥ|
devadevaṃ praṇamyeśaṃ pitaraṃ hyumayā saha|| 171.55||
babhāṣe vacanaṃ devaḥ kumāravararūpadhṛk|
śakreṇānena devendrā matsamakṣaṃ prabhāṣitam|| 171.56||
mahāṃstvatto 'aham ityeva tatra māṃ manyurāviśat|
tanmayaiṣā mahāśaktirnikhātā vasudhātale|| 171.57||
uddhartuṃ yo 'amaraḥ śakto muktvā devaṃ pinākinam|
utpāṭayatu sa hyetāṃ mahāṃ mattastato hi saḥ|| 171.58||
evam uktvā tato devo bālārkasadṛśaprabhaḥ|
tūṣṇīṃ babhūva hṛṣṭātmā tasthau ca pitṛpārśvataḥ|| 171.59||
athendro devatāmadhye rājyadarpānvito 'amaraḥ|
utpāṭayitum utsehe tāṃ śaktiṃ vasudhāṃ gatām|| 171.60||
na ca cālayituṃ śakto yatnādapi surādhipaḥ|
atha lajjānvito 'atyarthaṃ tasmāddeśādapākramat|| 171.61||
tato 'anye daivataśreṣṭhā yamānilapuraḥsarāḥ|
matiṃ cakruḥ samuddhartuṃ yatnaṃ śaktyāśca daṃśitāḥ (?)|| 171.62||
na ca cālayituṃ śekustāṃ śaktim amarottamāḥ|
tato viṣṇurameyātmā devān dṛṣṭvā hataujasaḥ|| 171.63||
śaktim uddhartum utsehe samakṣaṃ tridivaukasām|
tenāsau cālyamānāpi yasmācchaktirdharātale|| 171.64||
na cacāla mahāvīryā skandatejobalānvitā|
tato viṣṇurameyātmā jñātvā tattvārtham ādṛtaḥ|| 171.65||
kumāraṃ pūjayan bhaktyā śaktyutkṣepānnyavartata|
atha sarve 'amarā vyāsa viṣṇuśca surasattamaḥ|| 171.66||
saṃstutya ṣaṇmukhaṃ devam idam āhurmahaujasaḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- devānāṃ mahādevasutaḥ prabhuḥ|| 171.67||
nāthaḥ pālayitā sraṣṭā ārtighnaḥ pravaro mahān|
tvayā nāthena deveśa vayaṃ sarve sunirvṛtāḥ|| 171.68||
tiṣṭhāmaḥ sahitāḥ sarve tvam asmān pāhi sarvataḥ|
śakravyatikramaṃ caiva bāliśyānmohakāritam|| 171.69||
praṇayādyācito 'asmābhiḥ kṣantum arhasi sarvadā|
evaṃ sa bhagavān sarvaiḥ kumāraḥ saṃstuto 'amaraiḥ|| 171.70||
krodhaṃ tatyāja śakre tu tutoṣa ca divaukasām|
tataste girayaḥ sarve devī ca himavatsutā|| 171.71||
devarājastathā śakro hṛṣṭā guham apūjayan|
bhagavānapi saṃtuṣṭastanayāya varān dadau|| 171.72||
yayau cāpi gireḥ śṛṅgaṃ divyaṃ himavataḥ śubham|
sārdhaṃ guhena devyā ca mātR̥ṇāṃ gaṇanāyakaḥ|| 171.73||
krauñcena sahitāścāpi meruvindhyādayo 'acalāḥ|
śakraśca surarāḍdevaḥ svāni sadmāni bhejire|| 171.74||
evam etadyathā krauñcaḥ krauñcasārasavāsinaḥ|
guhena dāritaḥ śaktyā paścāccaiva kṛto 'amaraḥ|| 171.75||
dṛśyate cāpi tat krauñce kṣataṃ śaktyācalottame|
naikadaivatasaṃvāsaṃ yadabhūta vistṛtaṃ mahat|| 171.76||
etat te kathitaṃ sarvaṃ krauñcadāraṇam adbhutam|
ya imaṃ śṛṇuyānmartyaḥ sarvapāpaiḥ sa mucyate|| 171.77||
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan parameśāno mātR̥ṇāṃ nāyakaḥ katham|
kā etā mātaraścāpi śaṃsaitat pṛcchato mama|| 171.78||
kathaṃ mātṛgaṇā jātāḥ kiṃnimittam athāpi ca|
kiṃvīryāḥ kimprabhāvāśca sambhutāste gaṇāḥ prabho|| 171.79||
kaścāsām āśrayastena vartante tadgaṇāḥ śubhāḥ|
kena sṛṣṭāḥ svayaṃ vāpi etadicchāmi veditum|| 171.80||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
atra te vartayiṣyāmi mātR̥ṇām udbhavaṃ śubham|
purā hi bhagavān brahmā sṛṣṭvemā vividhāḥ prajāḥ|| 171.81||
avekṣamāṇaḥ kāleya cacāra vibudheśvaraḥ|
sa kadācit prajādhyakṣaḥ saṃdhyākāla upāgate|| 171.82||
deśaṃ ramyaṃ samāsādya tīre pūrvamahodadheḥ|
ramye cakāra saṃdhyāṃ hi varṣakoṭim atandritaḥ|| 171.83||
kṛtasaṃdhyastato devaḥ kamalāsanasaṃsthitaḥ|
cintayāmāsa ramyo 'ayaṃ deśo dṛṣṭimanoharaḥ|| 171.84||
karomyatra puraṃ ramyaṃ sarvakāmasamanvitam|
iti saṃcintya sa vyāsa bhagavān sarvasṛk prabhuḥ|| 171.85||
tasmin ramye pradeśe tu cakre puram anuttamam|
lohitāsitasauvarṇaiḥ prastaraiścāmitaprabham|| 171.86||
aṭṭāṭṭahāsakaiścaiva khātakaiśca samanvitam|
śṛṅgāṭakacatuṣkeṇa catuṣpādam iva sthitam|| 171.87||
vaprakhātakasaṃyuktairgṛhaiścāpi mahādhanaiḥ|
madhye mandākinī vāpī sariddivyā manoharā|| 171.88||
nalinīvanasaṃchannā prahṛṣṭakhaganāditā|
tat sṛṣṭvā tu puraṃ brahmā sauvarṇaṃ maṇibhūṣitam|| 171.89||
provāca vacanaṃ vyāsa paramādbhutam arthavat|
ramye puravare ye 'asmin vatsyanti sukṛtāśinaḥ|| 171.90||
avadhyāste jarāhīnāstejobalasamanvitāḥ|
bhaviṣyanti mahābhāgā matprasādānna saṃśayaḥ|| 171.91||
tataḥ sa bhagavān deva uvāca punareva ha|
asmin sadaiva kāmānām iṣṭānāṃ surasattamaḥ|| 171.92||
devo varṣati koṭiṃ vai tenāsmin sukhino janāḥ|
evaṃ sa bhagavānuktvā brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ|
agacchat svasabhāṃ divyāṃ naikasiddhaniṣevitām|| 171.93||
tasmin gate tato vyāsa asurairdaityabhāṣitaiḥ (?)}|
adhiṣṭhitaṃ puraṃ tadvai sarvairbrāhmaṇakaṇṭakaiḥ|| 171.94||
yeṣāṃ patirasukrodhaḥ sarvaśastrabhṛtāṃ varaḥ|
brahmahā yajñahā vipra devāntakasurāntakaḥ|| 171.95||
siṃhanādo bhīmanādo mada ityevamādayaḥ|
atha daityāḥ samāgamya haimakuṇḍapuraḥsarāḥ|
tasmin puravare sthitvā pīḍāṃ cakruranekaśaḥ|| 171.96||
dveṣṭāro jagataste hi jaghnurviprān sahasraśaḥ|
yajñahomādikāśchinnāḥ kriyāstairasurādhamaiḥ|| 171.97||
tānevaṃkāriṇo jñātvā sarva eva divaukasaḥ|
brahmalokam athābhyetya sarvam aśrāvayan vibhoḥ|| 171.98||
vaco divaukasāṃ śrutvā jñātvā daityaviceṣṭitam|
naitacchakyaṃ mayetyuktvā brahmā sārdhaṃ surottamaiḥ|| 171.99||
ājagāma bhavaṃ draṣṭuṃ ramyaṃ hīmagirervanam|
yatra gaurī tapastepe bhartṛdehārdhadhāriṇī|| 171.100||
praviṣṭāstatra te devā brahmādyāḥ sarva eva hi|
striya evābhavaṃstūrṇaṃ pārvatyāstapaso balāt|| 171.101||
tatastān devadeveśaḥ strībhūtān hi surottamān|
kimartham āgatā yūyam iti papraccha śūladhṛk|| 171.102||
tataste sahitāḥ sarve pūrvaṃ daityavimardanam|
nivedya śambhave paścāt kṛcchraṃ strībhāvam ātmanaḥ|| 171.103||
yathaivaṃ puruṣāḥ pūrvaṃ bhavāma iti te 'abruvan|
tānuvācātha deveśaḥ surān strībhāvam āgatān|| 171.104||
yāta yūyaṃ surāḥ sarve striyo bhūtvāsurāntikam|
strīṇām eva hi te vadhyā dānavā baladarpitāḥ|| 171.105||
tanūrmūrtimatīḥ kṛtvā parato mātaraḥ śubhāḥ|
ye ya eva yathā pūrvaṃ bhaviṣyatha surottamāḥ|| 171.106||
atha bhūyaḥ praṇamyeśaṃ devatā idam abruvan|
ātmano 'api tanuṃ deva kuru mūrtimatīṃ striyam|| 171.107||
yayā sārdhaṃ balāddaityān haṃsyāmaḥ parameśvara|
tato devo 'asṛjaddevīṃ rudrāṇīṃ mātaraṃ śubhām|| 171.108||
vikṛtaṃ rūpam āsthāya dvitīyām api mātaram|
nāmnā tu bahumāṃsāṃ tāṃ jagatsaṃhārarūpiṇīm|| 171.109||
niyogāddevadevasya tato viṣṇurapi prabhuḥ|
mātarāvasṛjaddve tu vārāhīṃ vaiṣṇavīm api|
abhūt pitāmahādbrāhmī śarvāṇī śaṃkarādapi|| 171.110||
kaumārī ṣaṇmukhāccāpi viṣṇorapi ca vaiṣṇavī|
vārāhi mādhavāddevī māhendrī ca purandarāt|| 171.111||
sarvatejomayī devī mātR̥ṇāṃ pravarā śubhā|
bahumāṃsā mahāvidyā babhūva vṛṣabhadhvajāt|| 171.112||
sarvāsāṃ devatānāṃ ca dehebhyo mātaraḥ śubhāḥ|
svarūpabaladhāriṇyo nirjagmurdaityanāśanāḥ|| 171.113||
vāyavyā vāruṇī yāmyā kauberī ca mahābalāḥ|
mahākālī tathāgneyī anyāścaiva sahasraśaḥ|| 171.114||
tā gatvā tat puraṃ ramyaṃ daityān bhīmaparākramān|
jaghnurbahuvidhaṃ devyo ghoranādairvibhīṣaṇaiḥ|| 171.115||
daityahīnaṃ ca taccakruḥ purāgryaṃ hemabhūṣitam|
atha daityairhataiḥ sarvairdevadeva umāpatiḥ|| 171.116||
ājagāma pradeśaṃ taṃ mātR̥ṇāṃ varaditsayā|
tān dṛṣṭvā nihatān sarvān daityānamaravidviṣaḥ|| 171.117||
parituṣṭastadā tāsāṃ varān prādādvṛṣadhvajaḥ|
jagato mātaro yūyaṃ mātṛbhūtā bhaviṣyathaḥ|| 171.118||
yuṣmākaṃ ye bhaviṣyanti bhaktāḥ puruṣapuṅgavāḥ|
striyo vāpi mahābhāgā na tān hiṃsanti hiṃsakāḥ|| 171.119||
mṛtā mama gaṇāścāpi bhaviṣyantyajarāmarāḥ|
bhavatīnām idaṃ sthānaṃ koṭīvarṣam iti śrutam|| 171.120||
bhaviṣyati jagatkhyātaṃ sarvapāpapramocanam|
ahaṃ heturhi yuṣmākaṃ yasmāt sṛṣṭā mayaiva ca|| 171.121||
hetukeśvaranāmnāhaṃ sthāsyāmyatra varapradaḥ|
yuṣmābhiḥ saha vatsyāmi nāyakatve vyavasthitaḥ|| 171.122||
yastu yuṣmān mayā sārdhaṃ vidhivat pūjayiṣyati|
sarvapāpavimuktātmā sa parāṃ gatim āpsyati|| 171.123||
dānavā nihatā yasmācchūlena bahumāṃsayā|
śūlakuṇḍam idaṃ nāmnā khyātaṃ tīrthaṃ bhaviṣyati|| 171.124||
iha śūlodakaṃ pītvā bahumāṃsāṃ praṇamya ca|
adhṛṣyaḥ sarvahiṃsrāṇāṃ bhaviṣyati narottamaḥ|| 171.125||
pratikūleti vikhyātā ramyā mandākinī nadī|
rudhiraughavatī seha bhavatīnāṃ bhaviṣyati|| 171.126||
ahaṃ brahmā ca viṣṇuśca ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
mātṛtantrāṇi divyāni mātṛyajñavidhiṃ param|| 171.127||
puṇyāni prakariṣyāmo yajanaṃ yairavāpsyatha|
brāhmaṃ svāyambhuvaṃ caiva kaumāraṃ yāmalaṃ tathā|| 171.128||
sārasvataṃ sa gāndhāram aiśānaṃ nandiyāmalam|
tantrāṇyetāni yuṣmākaṃ tathānyāni sahasraśaḥ|| 171.129||
bhaviṣyanti narā yaistu yuṣmān yakṣyanti bhaktitaḥ|
narāṇāṃ yajamānānāṃ varān yūyaṃ pradāsyatha|| 171.130||
divyasiddhipradā devyo divyayogā bhaviṣyatha|
yāśca nāryaḥ sadā yuṣmān yakṣyante sarahasyataḥ|| 171.131||
yogeśvaryo bhaviṣyanti rāmā divyaparākramāḥ|
chagalaḥ kumbhakarṇaśca madīyau gaṇanāyakau|| 171.132||
yuṣmākaṃ dvārapālatve sthāsyatastau mamājñayā|
koṭīvarṣam idaṃ sthānaṃ mātR̥ṇāṃ priyam uttamam|| 171.133||
śmaśānaṃ pravaraṃ divyaṃ bhaviṣyati sukhapradam|
varānevaṃ hi tā/llabdhvā mātaro lokamātaraḥ|| 171.134||
bhaktyā praṇamya deveśaṃ mumudurbhṛśam arditāḥ|
tataḥ prabhṛti tāḥ sarvāḥ sahitāḥ śaśimaulinā|| 171.135||
koṭīvarṣe vasanti sma sarvalokābhayapradāḥ|
evaṃ sa bhagavān devo mātR̥ṇāṃ gaṇanāyakaḥ|
abhavacchaṃkaro vyāsa yanmāṃ tvaṃ pṛṣṭavānasi|| 171.136||
utpattim etāṃ jagatīśvarīṇāṃ brahmendraśakrānilavanditānām|
paṭhenmanuṣyaḥ śṛṇuyācca nityaṃ yaḥ svargalokaṃ sa mṛto labheta|| 171.137||
|| iti skandapurāṇe
ekasaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 171.171||

dvisaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śakreṇa girayaḥ pūrvaṃ chinnapakṣā yathā kṛtāḥ|
tat pravakṣyāmi te vyāsa śṛṇu sarvam aśeṣataḥ|| 172.1||
purā siṃhavapuḥ kṛtvā viṣṇunā paramaujasā|
daityadānavanāthe tu hiraṇyakaśipau hate|| 172.2||
prahrādastatsuto daityo viṣṇuṃ prati cukopa ha|
hate pitari sa śrīmān mahādaityapatīśvaraḥ|| 172.3||
bahūnyabdasahasrāṇi cakārograṃ mahātapaḥ|
atha devaścaturvaktrastuṣṭastam asurādhipam|| 172.4||
provāca svayam āgatya varado 'asmīti sādaram|
praṇamyovāca varadam idaṃ brahmāṇam āgatam|| 172.5||
prahlādo manyutaptāṅgaḥ piturvadham anusmaran|
bhagavan yadi tuṣṭo 'asi varadaśca samāgataḥ|| 172.6||
rājānaṃ hatavān viṣṇuḥ pitaraṃ mama māyayā|
saṃgrāme tam ahaṃ viṣṇuṃ yathā hanyāṃ tathā kuru|| 172.7||
tam uvāca tato brahmā prahlādam asurottamam|
ajayyaḥ samare viṣṇuravadhyaśca surāsuraiḥ|| 172.8||
prasādāddevadevasya jagatsraṣṭurumāpateḥ|
naiṣa śakyo mayā dātuṃ varastubhyaṃ mahāsura|| 172.9||
anyaṃ vṛṇu yatheṣṭaṃ tvaṃ varaṃ yāvaddadāmi te|
cintayitvā tato bhūyo mahābuddhirmahāsuraḥ|| 172.10||
provāca vacanaṃ devaṃ kamalāsanasaṃsthitam|
ajayyo yadyavadhyaśca sa viṣṇurdevasattamaḥ|| 172.11||
tasya viṣṇostato deva śakrasyānyasya vā ripoḥ|
avadhyo 'aham ajayyaśca sambhaveyaṃ tavājñayā|| 172.12||
evam astviti taṃ brahmā procya dānavasattamam|
divyapadmāsano devastatraivāntaradhīyata|| 172.13||
prahlādo 'api varaṃ labdhvā brahmaṇaḥ paramādbhutam|
paścimasyodadhestīre tasthau cintākulendriyaḥ|| 172.14||
kathaṃ hanyām ahaṃ viṣṇuṃ śakraṃ caiva śatakratum|
evaṃ cintayatastasya prahlādasya suradviṣaḥ|| 172.15||
sarvaśailādhipaḥ śrīmāṃścakramaddhimavān giriḥ|
dvābhyām utpatya pakṣābhyām ājagāma viyaccaraḥ|| 172.16||
purā hi girayo vyāsa āsan pakṣasamanvitāḥ|
divyā viyadgamāḥ sarve sarvalokacarāstathā|| 172.17||
tam āgatam atho dṛṣṭvā prahrādo himavadgirim|
prāhedaṃ vacanaṃ prītaḥ kṛtvā svāgatam āditaḥ|| 172.18||
kaśyapasya vayaṃ pautrā daityā girivarādhipa|
bhavanto 'api sutāstasya devā api mahāgire|| 172.19||
asmākaṃ bhavatāṃ caiva ekasmāt sambhavo gire|
devatā bhrātaro bhūtvā asmākaṃ devatāśca hi|| 172.20||
avamanyāsurānasmān rājyaṃ kurvanti darpitāḥ|
vayaṃ yūyaṃ ca saṃgatya jitvā devānaśeṣataḥ|
trailokyaṃ sarvam ākramya rājyaṃ kurmo mahāgire|| 172.21||
devānāṃ yajanaṃ yeṣu hūyante yeṣu cāgnayaḥ|
prīyante devatā yeṣu deśāṃstānacaleśvara|| 172.22||
sahitaḥ sarvaśailaistvam ākramya tvaritaṃ jahi|
ijyāhīnāṃstato devān sukhaṃ haṃsyāma nirvṛtāḥ|| 172.23||
ityukto daityarājena himavānacalottamaḥ|
naitadyuktam iti prāha sāśaṅko dānavādhipam|| 172.24||
punareva tataḥ prāha himavantaṃ mahāsuraḥ|
matto yuktaṃ paraṃ tvaṃ cedyadi vetsi nagādhipa|| 172.25||
eṣa tvāṃ sahitaḥ śailairneṣyāmi nidhanaṃ samam|
apramattastadā tiṣṭha yāvat tvāṃ hanmi parvata|| 172.26||
daityarājaṃ tataḥ kruddhaṃ dṛṣṭvā parvatasattamaḥ|
karomyevam iti prāha tato daityastutoṣa saḥ|| 172.27||
atha śailaistadā sārdhaṃ himavānacalottamaḥ|
prahlādasya vacaḥ śrutvā cakre deśopamardanam|| 172.28||
pitṛdevātmikāḥ sarvā yajñahomādikāḥ kriyāḥ|
vartante yeṣu deśeṣu girayastān samākraman|| 172.29||
athotsanneṣu deśeṣu nārado munisattamaḥ|
śakrāyāśrāvayat sarvaṃ parvatānāṃ vyatikramam|| 172.30||
tacchrutvā krodhasantapto devarājaḥ śatakratuḥ|
samāgamyācalān prāha kim etaditi manyumān|| 172.31||
athocurgirayo vyāsa kruddhaṃ devagaṇādhipam|
prahlādasya bhayāddeva mahādaityapatervayam|| 172.32||
imaṃ vyatikramaṃ prāptā na doṣo naḥ kathaṃcana|
atha cenmanyase doṣam asmākam amarādhipa|| 172.33||
prahrādāntikam āgaccha prayāma sahitā drutam|
tenedaṃ kāritaṃ sarvaṃ yajñadeśopamardanam|
daityarājena balinā yuṣmadapriyalipsayā|| 172.34||
nāparādho 'ayam asmākaṃ tathā tvaṃ viddhi devapa|
tānevaṃ bruvataḥ śakraḥ sutarāṃ manyumān girīn|| 172.35||
pakṣahīnāṃstadā cakre kṣiptvā vajraṃ punaḥ punaḥ|
hīnapakṣāstataste tu sarva evācaleśvarāḥ|| 172.36||
peturmahītale vyāsa chinnapakṣāḥ khagā iva|
atha daityapatiḥ śrutvā prahrādo 'asurapuṅgavaḥ|| 172.37||
pakṣacchedaṃ nagendrāṇāṃ bhṛśaṃ cukrodha pīḍitaḥ|
kiṃ karomīti saṃcintya ciraṃ daityagaṇādhipaḥ|| 172.38||
badaryāśramam āgatya dadarśa viṣṇum āsthitam|
tasyāsīt sumahadyuddhaṃ viṣṇunā sārdham adbhutam|| 172.39||
na śaśāka ca taṃ viṣṇurjetuṃ prahlādam ojasā|
tayoryuddham abhūdghoraṃ divyam abdaśataṃ purā|| 172.40||
ātmānaṃ veda hīnaṃ ca viṣṇuḥ prahlādadānavāt|
so 'abhiyuktastadā yuddhe viṣṇuḥ paramadharmavit|| 172.41||
aśakto dānavaṃ jetuṃ manyumānabhavat prabhuḥ|
atha dhyātvā mahādevaṃ praṇamya ca punaḥ punaḥ|| 172.42||
sasmāra para -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- pinākinas|| 172.43||
avadhyatvam ajayyatvaṃ sarvalokanivāsibhiḥ|
prasādaṃ tam anusmṛtya śaivaṃ viṣṇuḥ surottamaḥ|| 172.44||
mahāsattvabalo bhūtvā daityam abhyadravadbalī|
hīyamānam athātmānaṃ hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ|| 172.45||
jñātvā ca balinaṃ viṣṇuṃ yuddhadeśādapākramat|
ajitaṃ viṣṇunātmānaṃ śivatejovimohitaḥ|| 172.46||
prahrādo jitam ātmānaṃ bubudhe dānaveśvaraḥ|
brahmaṇo 'api varaṃ labdhvā ajayyatvam athātmanaḥ|| 172.47||
jitam eva tadātmānam amanyata mahāsuraḥ|
prahrādāsurasaṃgrāmaṃ ghoraṃ devabhayaṃkaram|| 172.48||
abhūdabdaśataṃ divyaṃ viṣṇunā sārdham adbhutam|
na śrutena na vīryeṇa na śauryeṇa na tejasā|| 172.49||
na buddhyā na ca dharmeṇa prahrādasadṛśo 'asuraḥ|
hiraṇyakaśipurnāsīdrājā tatsadṛśo mahān|| 172.50||
nāndhako na hiraṇyākṣaḥ prahlādasadṛśo bale|
bhṛguśāpāt kilāyāto daityatvaṃ viṣṇureva saḥ|| 172.51||
śauryeṇa spṛhayanti sma śrutena vinayena ca|
divaukaso 'api saṃsiddhāḥ prahrādasya mahātmanaḥ|| 172.52||
nābhavaṃstasya rājye tu duḥkhaśokānvitāḥ prajāḥ|
evaṃ sa dānavaśreṣṭhaḥ kṛtvā yuddhaṃ tu viṣṇunā|| 172.53||
paścāttāpopataptāṅgo viṣayebhyo gataspṛhaḥ|
varadānam anityaṃ tajjñātvā ca tapasaḥ phalam|| 172.54||
niḥspṛhaḥ sarvakāryeṣu viṣayepsāvivarjitaḥ|
sarvasannyastakarmā tu dhyānābhyāsaparāyaṇaḥ|| 172.55||
pravavrāja mahādaityaḥ śamepsurmokṣasiddhaye|
punarāvartakaṃ janma buddhvā cānityatāṃ parām|| 172.56||
kaṣṭaṃ rājyam iti jñātvā prahrādaḥ paramārthavit|
abhiṣicya sutaṃ rājye ditijānāṃ virocanam|| 172.57||
daityadānavarājānaṃ kṛtvā tam asureśvaram|
mokṣasiddhiṃ parām icchan pravrajyākṛtaniścayaḥ|| 172.58||
paraṃ tattvam athānveṣṭuṃ guṇātītam ajaṃ śivam|
sākṣādbhagavataḥ śiṣyaṃ kapilasyāsuriṃ munim|| 172.59||
śiṣyatvenopasaṃgamya mokṣavidyām avāptavān|
prakṛtīnāṃ paraṃ tattvaṃ vikārāṇāṃ paraṃ tathā|| 172.60||
kṣetrajñaṃ puruṣaṃ jñātvā bhoktāraṃ bhoktṛvarjitam|
mokṣavidyāparārthajñaḥ sāṃkhyasiddhāntapāragaḥ|| 172.61||
siddhaḥ pañcaśikho nāmnā so 'abhavanmunisattama|
sa yogaṃ paramaṃ labdhvā sāṃkhyācāryo mahāmuniḥ|
duḥkhatrayavinirmuktaḥ prāptavān padam avyayam|| 172.62||
śrīmānevaṃ tribhuvanaripurdaityarājo mahātmā
kṛtvā vairaṃ vibudhaguruṇā viṣṇunā dīrghakālam|
siddhaḥ paścājjagadabhayadaḥ prāptayogaśca bhūtvā
muktaḥ paścāt sa padam amṛtaṃ brahma cādyaṃ hyavāpa|| 172.63||
kṣetrajñaboddhā guṇaviprayukto duḥkhairvihīno bhavapāśabandhaiḥ|
tāmisramohapratibandhamukto yogīśvaro 'asau ditijādhipo 'abhūt|| 172.64||
evaṃ tāṃśchinnapakṣāṃstu girīn sarvān purandaraḥ|
pracakāra muniśreṣṭha prāk pṛṣṭo yadahaṃ tvayā|| 172.65||
|| iti skandapurāṇe prahrādacarite parvatapakṣacchedo nāmā
dvisaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 172.172||

trisaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
nagendre jīvite krauñce toṣite ca surairguhe|
yāto himavataḥ śṛṅgaṃ pārvatyā sahito haraḥ|| 173.1||
kim anyadakaroddevaḥ kiṃ cainaṃ prāha pārvatī|
etat kathaya viprendra na tṛptiḥ śṛṇvato hi me|| 173.2||
sūta uvāca|
evam ukto munīdreṇa brahmaṇastanayo 'avyayaḥ|
ṛṣiḥ paramayogīśaḥ kathayāmāsa tattvataḥ|| 173.3||
prayāte himavacchṛṅgaṃ devadeve sahomayā|
babhāṣe girijā devaṃ praṇamya parameśvaram|| 173.4||
uñchavṛtterhiraṇyasya naimiśāraṇyavāsinaḥ|
śaucena tapasā bhaktyā yuktasya ca śamena hi|| 173.5||
svayam eva prayātāhaṃ dvijaṃ pūjāṃ pratīcchitum|
māhātmyaṃ tasya taddṛṣṭvā brāhmaṇasya tapasvinaḥ|| 173.6||
gatāhaṃ vismayaṃ deva dvijāḥ śreṣṭhatamā iti|
devebhyo 'api garīyāṃso brāhmaṇā iti me matiḥ|
tvatto 'atha śrotum icchāmi dvijamāhātmyam uttamam|| 173.7||
devadeva uvāca|
evam etajjagaddhātri surāsuranamaskṛte|
śreṣṭhāstapasvino viprā devebhyo 'api garīyasaḥ|| 173.8||
madīyā yāḥ prajāḥ sṛṣṭāḥ prathamāḥ prabhavo hyaham|
rudrā dvijātayaḥ pūrvaṃ mayā sṛṣṭā mahaujasaḥ|| 173.9||
madīyāṃ sṛṣṭim ālokya brahmaṇāpi sisṛkṣuṇā|
brāhmaṇā mūrdhataḥ sṛṣṭāḥ pūrvam eva mahāprabhāḥ|| 173.10||
agrabhūto hyahaṃ teṣāṃ dvijaśreṣṭhastadābhavam|
tataste matsakhāḥ sarve babhūvurviprasattamāḥ|| 173.11||
uttamaiṣāparā sṛṣṭirbrāhmaṇāḥ parameṣṭhinaḥ|
dharmādikaṃ caturvargaṃ sarvaṃ teṣu pratiṣṭhitam|| 173.12||
yajjuhvati havirviprāstena tṛpyanti devatāḥ|
jagat pratiṣṭhitaṃ sarvaṃ brāhmaṇānāṃ hi tejasā|| 173.13||
mṛtyujanmāpahaṃ yat tanmama pāśupataṃ vratam|
na varṇāḥ sādhayantyanye muktvā brāhmaṇasattamān|| 173.14||
lakṣaṇaṃ sampravakṣyāmi dvijātīnām idaṃ śṛṇu|
śaucārjavavidhānaṃ ca prabhāvaṃ karma caiva ha|| 173.15||
brāhmaṇastu bhavejjātyā saṃskārāddvija ucyate|
vidyayā vipratāṃ yāti brāhmaṇyaṃ trividhaṃ smṛtam|| 173.16||
yaśca jātyā bhavedvipro yaśca syādvedapāragaḥ|
tayostrāṇe vadhe cāpi puṇyapāpe same smṛte|| 173.17||
jātyā ca yo bhavedvipraḥ sarvāgamaviśāradaḥ|
tapaḥśaucasamāyuktastryavadātaḥ sa ucyate|| 173.18||
tādṛśaṃ bhojayecchrāddhe daive karmaṇi vāpi yaḥ|
akṣayaṃ tadbhavet tasya tryavadātasya tarpaṇāt|| 173.19||
vedavidyo bhavedvipro nityaṃ homaparāyaṇaḥ|
so 'api śreṣṭhaḥ smṛto devi pūjitastārayet kulam|| 173.20||
sarvathā jātimātreṇa yo 'api syādbrāhmaṇaḥ kvacit|
so 'api lokagururdevi pūjitaḥ svargado bhavet|| 173.21||
agnihotraṃ tapo yajñaḥ śaucam ārjavam eva ca|
satyaṃ vedaprasaṅgaśca dvijakarma paraṃ smṛtam|| 173.22||
nānṛtaṃ brāhmaṇo brūte na hanti prāṇinaṃ dvijaḥ|
na sevāṃ kurute vipro na dvijaḥ pāpakṛdbhavet|| 173.23||
brāhmaṇaśca tapasvī ca na janma punarāpnute|
vidvadbrāhmaṇatāṃ labdhvā kiṃ na labdhaṃ hi dehinā|| 173.24||
mūrtayo yāḥ smṛtā hyaṣṭāvarkasomādayo mama|
sarvāstā nivasanti sma brāhmaṇe tapasaidhite|| 173.25||
dvijatejo hyavaṣṭabhya amṛtaṃ gāva eva ca|
prabhavanti sadā devi viprāḥ śreṣṭhatamāstataḥ|| 173.26||
nāsādhyaṃ vidyate teṣāṃ dvijānāṃ paramaujasām|
ruṣitāste prasannā vā prayacchanti śubhāśubham|| 173.27||
dvijās=tapasvino ye tu vedavidyāviśāradāḥ|
muktidāstu bhaveyuste devānām api devatāḥ|| 173.28||
ahaṃ pitāmahaścaiva teṣāṃ yonidvayaṃ smṛtam|
mattaḥ pūrvaṃ prasūtāste tato devi pitāmahāt|| 173.29||
āvāṃ hetū dvijātīnāṃ prakṛtitvāt tvam eva ca|
prakṛtistvaṃ samākhyātā puruṣaḥ paramo hyaham|| 173.30||
brahmaviṣṇū smṛtau yau tau rajaḥsattvaguṇātmakau|
āvābhyāṃ tau prajāyete sṛṣṭikāle prajāpatī|| 173.31||
ahaṃ hyagnistamo viṣṇuḥ sattvaṃ brahmaṇi saṃsthitam|
rajastvaṃ vyāpitaṃ viddhi guṇabhūteṣu karmasu|| 173.32||
mohātmakau smṛtāvetau tamo rāgastathaiva ca|
sattvaṃ nāśayate tau hi sa cāgneḥ samprajāyate|| 173.33||
vahnitejāḥ smṛtā hyete mahātmāno dvijātayaḥ|
sarvataḥ prabhavantyete nāsti teṣāṃ nivāraṇam|| 173.34||
ārjavaṃ samatāṃ caiva viddhi tejo dvijātiṣu|
tapovidyāsamāyuktādārjavastu viśiṣyate|| 173.35||
aśāṭhyaṃ hanti pāpāni samatā mohabandhanam|
ubhe 'apyete nihanti sma ārjavaṃ sevitaṃ dvijaiḥ|| 173.36||
purā bhāgīrathītīre dvijaḥ paramadharmavit|
nāmnā dānarucirnāma uñchavṛttirbabhūva ha|| 173.37||
sarvavidyāvinītātmā sarvabhūtābhayapradaḥ|
saha patnyā ca madbhakto vahnihomaparāyaṇaḥ|| 173.38||
atithiṃ bhojayitvā ca pūrvaṃ devi yathāgatam|
ṣaṣṭhe kāle tato 'aśnāti tasyedaṃ vratam uttamam|| 173.39||
athaivaṃ vartamānasya bhūyān kālo jagāma ha|
atithau āgate tasya na vikalpaḥ prajāyate|| 173.40||
tapaḥśaucasamāyukta ārjavaikarato dvijaḥ|
babhūvātyartham arciṣmānarkāgnī iva tejasā|| 173.41||
tasyaivaṃ tapaso vahniḥ prītastuṣṭim agāt parām|
śubhaditsurabhūccāsya samīhitaphalapradaḥ|| 173.42||
kadācidatha kālena ṣaṣṭhe kāle samāgate|
himamegholvaṇe śīte durdine paryaṭan dvijaḥ|| 173.43||
nāpaśyadatithiṃ kaṃcidbubhukṣāklamakheditaḥ|
yadā nāsāditastena dinānte 'apyatithiḥ kvacit|| 173.44||
aprāśyaiva tadā kiṃcidupavāsaparāyaṇaḥ|
babhūva dvijamukhyo 'asau nātmakhedam acintayat|| 173.45||
patnyapyasya mahābhāgā patibhaktivrate ratā|
yathaivāsyāḥ patiścakre tathā sāpyakarot tadā|| 173.46||
śītakṣudupataptāṅgo naikadvandvasamāvṛtaḥ|
kleśena mahatātīva khinno 'abhūddevi sa dvijaḥ|| 173.47||
dvitīye 'atha samāyāte ṣaṣṭhe kāle sa ha dvijaḥ|
śītadurdinajāddoṣānnaivātithim avaikṣata|| 173.48||
athāgnistasya tajjñātvā niścayaṃ paramaṃ mahat|
śvapākasadṛśaṃ rūpaṃ vikṛtaṃ kutsitaṃ ca hi|| 173.49||
kṛtvā pādapamūlasthaḥ pradadau tasya dar'sanam|
kṣudhārto 'atha sa viprendraḥ paryaṭannatithīpsayā|| 173.50||
apaśyadvṛkṣamūlasthaṃ ghoraṃ vikṛtarūpiṇam|
śvapākaṃ śītasaṃkhinnaṃ naikavraṇaśatāṅkitam|| 173.51||
durdṛśaṃ vṛddham ārtaṃ ca prasravatkṛmiśoṇitam|
vikrośantaṃ ca tāteti so 'apaśyaddvijasattamaḥ|| 173.52||
kṛpaṇaṃ tam atho dṛṣṭvā śvapākaṃ dvijasattamaḥ|
samāśvasihi bhadreti provāca madhuraṃ vacaḥ|| 173.53||
śītāpanayanārthaṃ ca vahnim asyānayaddvijaḥ|
atha taṃ vahnisaṃsargāt samāśvastam uvāca saḥ|| 173.54||
ehi bhuṅkṣvātithirme tvaṃ bhava bhadreti sādaram|
tam uvāca tato dīnaṃ śvapākastapasāṃ nidhim|| 173.55||
śvapāko 'ahaṃ dvijaśreṣṭha mahyam annam ihaiva hi|
kutsitāya prayacchasva yathaiva mṛgapakṣiṇām|| 173.56||
nāhaṃ saṃskṛtam āhartuṃ yogyo 'annam iti cābravīt|
tam evaṃvādinaṃ dhyānājjñātvā vahnim upasthitam|| 173.57||
provāca dvijaśārdūla idaṃ vacanakovidaḥ|
nāhaṃ jātiṃ garhayāmi pūjayāmi na cānagha|| 173.58||
ātmā sarvagato hyeṣa sarvaprāṇiṣu saṃsthitaḥ|
ātmānaṃ tam ahaṃ bhaktyā pūjayāmi paraṃ śivam|| 173.59||
sarvatra saṃsthitaṃ matvā puruṣaṃ parameśvaram|
tiryakṣu na hi me kutsā tvadvidheṣu viśeṣataḥ|| 173.60||
sarvam eva sa eveti tapaḥśaucaparāyaṇaḥ|
pūjayāmyaham avyagrastatra niḥsaṃśayo bhava|| 173.61||
kṛmikīṭākhusarpeṣu śvapāgdevadvijātiṣu|
yadā sarvagato hi ātmā tadā kutsā kathaṃ ca naḥ|| 173.62||
na hi me kutsito bhadra ehi me tvam akutsitaḥ|
bhuṅkṣva saṃskṛtam annaṃ tu prāpayāsmānanugraham|| 173.63||
evam ukto dvijendreṇa śvapākaḥ prītimāṃstadā|
gṛhaṃ jagāma viprasya tasyānugrahalipsayā|| 173.64||
atha dānarucistasya atitheriva pūjitam|
ātithyaṃ vidhivaccakre bhāvaśuddhena cetasā|| 173.65||
mūrtimān so 'abhavat prīto bhojito havyavāhanaḥ|
pradadau īpsitaṃ cāsmai yogaiśvaryam anuttamam|| 173.66||
sa yogaṃ paramaṃ prāpya uñchavṛttirdvijottamaḥ|
vimuktaḥ saha patnyā tu prāptavānamṛtaṃ padam|| 173.67||
yathaiva kapilaḥ siddhastattvavit paramo muniḥ|
evam ārjavasampanno brāhmaṇaḥ kṛtalakṣaṇaḥ|
na kiṃcinnāpnuyāddevi śubhācchubhataraṃ padam|| 173.68||
etat te kathitaṃ nagendratanaye māhātmyam agryaṃ paraṃ
śṛṇvan nityam idaṃ paṭhaṃśca vidhivadvidvāñchucirmānavaḥ|
māhātmyam etat kathitaṃ yathāvanmahāmahīdhrendrasute dvijānām|
sṛṣṭeḥ prabhavānmama te dvijendrā māhātmyam itthaṃ paramaṃ hyavāpuḥ|| 173.70||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
dvijamāhātmyam ullikhya pārvatīparameśayoḥ|
babhūvetthaṃ susaṃvādaḥ puṇyaḥ pāpavināśanaḥ|| 173.71||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- pārāśarya tapodhana|
śrotavyaṃ manyase mattastat pṛcchasva samāhitaḥ|| 173.72||
|| iti skandapurāṇe dvijamāhātmyavarṇanaṃ nāmā
trisaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 173.173||

catuḥsaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan yat tvayā proktaṃ dakṣayajñavadhe tadā|
prāpya pāśupataṃ yogaṃ brahmādyāstridivaukasaḥ|| 174.1||
lebhire paramaṃ tattvaṃ jñānena hi mahāmune|
tanme kathaya bhaktāya śiṣyāya paripṛcchate|| 174.2||
kīdṛśaṃ tat paraṃ yogaṃ jñānaṃ pāśupataṃ śubham|
yajjñātvā brāhmaṇāḥ siddhāḥ prāpnuyurmokṣam uttamam|
iti pṛṣṭastu śiṣyeṇa provāca munisattamaḥ|| 174.3||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
sādhu vyāsa mahābuddhe mumukṣurasi putraka|
yanmāṃ pṛcchasi tajjñānaṃ yogaṃ māheśvaraṃ param|| 174.4||
sarvāsāṃ yogavidyānāṃ yat tattvaṃ parikīrtyate|
sāṃkhyayogāgamopetāḥ sarvādhyātmaviśāradāḥ|| 174.5||
yogaiśvaryam api prāpya tattvaṃ naivopalebhire|
yad abuddhvā mahābhāga jñānaṃ śaṃkarabhāṣitam|| 174.6||
tadyathā kathitaṃ teṣāṃ tryambakeṇa divaukasām|
tat te 'ahaṃ saṃpravakṣyāmi saṃkṣepāt tattvaviniścayam|| 174.7||
vistareṇa na tacchakyaṃ vaktuṃ varṣaśatairapi|
tasyāhaṃ sthitapakṣaṃ tu saṃsārotpattināśanam|| 174.8||
muktisiddhipradaṃ vakṣye saṃkṣepānmatam uttamam|
namaskṛtya maheśānaṃ puruṣaṃ bhūtabhāvanam|| 174.9||
prakṛteḥ paramaṃ guhyaṃ pudgalaṃ parameṣṭhinam|
yaṃ sāṃkhyāḥ puruṣaṃ prāhuḥ pañcaviṃśam ajaṃ vibhum|| 174.10||
yogāścāpi hi ṣaḍviṃśaṃ vyāpinaṃ triguṇātmakam|
yo 'asṛjat sṛṣṭikāle tu devau sarvajagatsṛjau|| 174.11||
prajāpatī mahātmānau dhyātvā viṣṇupitāmahau|
taṃ praṇamya mahādevaṃ tryakṣaṃ varadam īśvaram|| 174.12||
pravakṣyāmi mataṃ tasya yogasiddhāntaniścayam|
lakṣaṇaṃ viddhi yogasya procyamānam idaṃ mayā|| 174.13||
chidyante paśupāśāni yasyābhyāsānmahāmune|
pratyayasya bahirlopo manasi ātmani saṃsthite|| 174.14||
abhisandhiḥ pare caiva īśvarasyātmanaśca ha|
eṣa bhoga iti vyāsa kīrtitaḥ śambhunā purā|| 174.15||
bhavajanmāpahaḥ sūkṣmaḥ prapannānāṃ divaukasām|
śarīre tiṣṭhataḥ puṃso yadātmani manaḥ sthitam|| 174.16||
avitarkaṃ bahiścaiva sūkṣmam abhyāsayojitam|
kṛtānāṃ pratyayaiḥ sūkṣmaiḥ sukhaduḥkhādisaṃjñinām|| 174.17||
aśeṣalopa ityuktaṃ sādhakasya tu yuñjataḥ|
paro maheśvaro devaḥ so 'abhisandhistu yojakaḥ|| 174.18||
abhisandhistadā yasmādīśvarasyātmanaśca ha|
sukhādānam athaikena bhāvanā -- -- yojanāt|| 174.19||
pra -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- tiṣṭhataḥ sataḥ|
sādhakasya bhavennityaṃ hyadriḥ siddham idaṃ phalam|| 174.20||
athādhikaraṇaṃ tatra kramaśaḥ parikīrtyate|
pratyāhāram ato vidyā prāṇāyamastathaiva ca|
dhyānaṃ ca dhāraṇā caiva yogābhyāsa udāhṛtaḥ|| 174.21||
tisro mṛtyum atikramya kriyā hi caturātmikāḥ|
vartante na ca vai -- -- rmṛtyuḥ prabhavate mune|| 174.22||
vaśyā hi dhātavastasmādbhavantyasya na saṃśayaḥ|
tato 'asau pavamṛtyuśca sādhako bhavati -- --|| 174.23||
imāstarkakriyā vyāsa mastake hṛdi caiva hi|
antarikṣe ca sarvāstu kīrtitā hi na saṃśayaḥ|| 174.24||
sthānatrayanibaddhāstu caturlakṣaṇasaṃsthitāḥ|
kriyāḥ pramādinā naitāḥ śakyāḥ sādhayituṃ kvacit|| 174.25||
tisra etāḥ sadā mṛtyuṃ pravṛttā mohalakṣaṇāḥ|
viyogo na bhavet tāsu kriyāstvekaka -- -- --|| 174.26||
ajñānaṃ kampate tāsu bahirantaścarāsvapi|
kriyāsu sādhako yuktastathā madhyagatāsu ca|| 174.27||
bhūtendriyamanaḥkāladiṅnivṛttiḥ prabhāvataḥ|
daśaivāśāstrayaḥ kālā bhūtānīndriyavistaraḥ|| 174.28||
manaḥpracārasaṃyukto viṣayābhāvalakṣaṇaḥ|
pratyāhāra iti proktaḥ purā bhagavatā svayam|| 174.29||
digantaragamābhāvānmanasyavicalasthitau|
pratyāhārasamutpattiryogotpattau sakṛdbhavet|| 174.30||
trikālaviṣayaṃ jñānam aiśvaryodayam eva ca|
cale manasi nābhūtāṃ bhavetāṃ saṃsthite samam|| 174.31||
manaḥ sarvam idaṃ yasmāt sādhanaṃ yogakarmaṇaḥ|
ekato manasaḥ sthāne tasmādyatnaṃ samācaret|| 174.32||
prāṇanigrahaṇe dhyānaṃ prāṇāyāmam iti smṛtam|
prāṇa eva hi vāyūnāṃ sārathye vartate sadā|| 174.33||
prāṇanigrahaṇe yogī nityam abhyāsam ācaret|
uttarottarasaṃsiddhyā vāyu -- -- -- gocare|| 174.34||
jyotiḥ pravartanaṃ vidyānnityam abhyāsayojitam|
dvirapāne sakṛt prāṇe samāne ca -- -- -- --|| 174.35||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 174.36||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
kumbha eṣa tṛtīyastu yogavahnipradīpakaḥ|| 174.37||
ebhirdhyānagatiḥ sūkṣmā vāyusaṃrodhakāritā|
pravartate yayā yogī paramaṃ veṣṭi pudgalam|| 174.38||
sakṛdeva samāhārādasakṛt parimokṣaṇāt|
kumbhakaṃ caitaduddiṣṭaṃ prāṇāyāmādidhāraṇāt|| 174.39||
prāṇo vāyurasau ātmā śarīre jīva -- -- --|
vidyādrūpadvayaṃ tasya sthūlaṃ sūkṣmaṃ ca sarvataḥ|| 174.40||
avyaktaṃ sūkṣmarūpaṃ tu sthūlam ākāralakṣaṇam|
sthūlādārabhya sūkṣmaṃ tu dhyānābhyāsānnirūpayet|| 174.41||
sūkṣmasaṃropaṇājjyotiḥ prakāśo jāyate mune|
dhyāyataḥ sthūlalakṣyaṃ tu sarvadikṣu sṛtaṃ manaḥ|
yadā dīptimadutpadyet tadāśu sthāpayet punaḥ|| 174.42||
girau vṛkṣe marutpṛṣṭhe śvabhre prāsādapaṅktiṣu|
samudre vasudhāyāṃ vā manaḥsaṃyogam ācaret|| 174.43||
sthāpitaṃ tanmanastatra punaḥ saṃhāram āvrajet|
acaitanyaṃ diśenmohādvāyurdṛṣṭam ato 'anyathā|| 174.44||
saṃhṛtya ca tato vyāpi bhūyo dhyānagatiṃ caret|
dhyāyato nityam abhyāsānmano vāyu -- -- -- --|| 174.45||
pravṛttajñānayogasya viṣayāsaṃgasaṃkṣaye|
prātibhāni hi vighnāni sattvādiguṇajāni tu|
vighnabhūtāni yogasya prodbhavanti hi yuñjataḥ|| 174.46||
tāni vidvān prayatnena viṣayecchāvivarjitaḥ|
jitvā nirvāṇamārgastho bhavet traiguṇyavarjitaḥ|| 174.47||
ākāśagamanaṃ divyam apsarogaṇasaṃgajam|
abhiṣekaśca devebhyaścitrakāvyapravartanam|| 174.48||
aiśvaryasukhasaṃsaktirhemaratnāgamaṃ bahu|
sattvādetāni vighnāni prātibhāni tu lakṣayet|| 174.49||
utpattimadayuktāni bhinnācārakramāṇi tu|
rajovighnāni saṃvidyāt prātibhāni na saṃśayaḥ|| 174.50||
kṣayaśūlajvaronmādakuṣṭhasarpagrahāṇi tu|
yātanodgamapūrvāṇi tāmasāni vinirdiśet|| 174.51||
guṇatrayasamutthāni prātibhāni sadā muniḥ|
yuñjan saṃlakṣayecchīghraṃ cikitsedāśu caiva hi|| 174.52||
prāṇādyānabhisaṃdhāya manaḥ saṃhṛtya caiva hi|
prāṇāyāmena kumbhena hanyādvighnāni sarvataḥ|| 174.53||
rajaḥ sattvaṃ tamaścaiva pradhānasya guṇāstrayaḥ|
tasyaiva hi maheśasya prajāsaṃsargahetavaḥ|| 174.54||
yogamohādbhavantyete sābhimānasya yuñjataḥ|
nirīho nirvṛto yogī sacetā ghaṭate yadā|| 174.55||
prātibhāni tadā yānti vighnāni hi samaṃ kṣayam|
prādurbhāvastatasteṣāṃ guṇānāṃ mohakāraṇam|| 174.56||
tamo raudraṃ vijānīyāt sattvaṃ brahmaṇi saṃsthitam|
rajastu vaiṣṇavaṃ vidyāt teṣāṃ hantā maheśvaraḥ|| 174.57||
mahādevaṃ paraṃ jñātvā yogābhyāsarato dvijaḥ|
guṇatrayavinirmuktaḥ śaṃkare layam āpnuyāt|| 174.58||
yamaiḥ saniyamaiḥ pūrvaṃ śodhayedātmanastanum|
tataḥ śāstrapraṇītena dharmādharmavivarjitaḥ|| 174.59||
krameṇa sopadeśena dhyānābhyāsaṃ samācaret|
śabdādīn viṣayān jitvā śrotrādīndriyagocarān|| 174.60||
samo daivatatiryakṣu nirmamaḥ sarvavastuṣu|
sarvārambhavinirmuktaḥ puṇyapāpavivarjitaḥ|| 174.61||
nirdvandvo nirjane deśe yogābhyāsaṃ samācaret|
sābhimānaṃ saniyamaṃ tyaktvā sāṃkhyaviniścayam|| 174.62||
pare māheśvare yoge nityam abhyāsam ācaret|
aṣṭau prakṛtayo nityā vikārāścaiva ṣoḍaśa|| 174.63||
puruṣaḥ pañcaviṃśaśca sāṃkhyasiddhāntagocaraḥ|
etadeva paraṃ guhyaṃ sāṃkhyānāṃ tattvaviniścaye|
prakṛterantaraṃ jñātvā puruṣasya ca mucyate|| 174.64||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatasyogavarṇanaṃ nāma dhyānavidhau
prathamo 'ayaṃ catuḥsaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 174.174||

pañcasaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
yogaṃ sāṃkhyaṃ ca sarvatra dvividhaṃ jñānam ucyate|
tatra sāṃkhyaratāḥ kecit kecidyogapathāśritāḥ|| 175.1||
avyaktaṃ prakṛtiścaiva tathāhaṃkāra eva ca|
aṣṭau prakṛtayo hyetāstanmātraiḥ pañcabhiḥ saha|| 175.2||
pañca buddhīndriyāṇi āhuḥ pañca karmendriyāṇi ca|
manaḥ pañca ca bhūtāni vikārāḥ ṣoḍaśa smṛtāḥ|| 175.3||
puruṣaḥ pañcaviṃśaśca sarvārambhavivarjitaḥ|
nityaḥ sarvagataḥ sūkṣmaścetāvāṃstriguṇojjhitaḥ|| 175.4||
saṃśuddho vimalo bhoktā akartā sākṣivat sthitaḥ|
viditvā na viśantyenaṃ bhūyaḥ saṃsārapañjaram|| 175.5||
pañcaviṃśati tattvāni sāṃkhyairetāni yogibhiḥ|
proktāni yadviditvā hi mucyate kila janmanaḥ|| 175.6||
sūkṣmā prakṛtiravyaktā bhojyā sarvaratā calā|
nityā cācetanā caiva vijñeyā sarvakāmikī|| 175.7||
tamaḥ sattvaṃ rajaśceti viṣayasthaṃ guṇatrayam|
yeṣām avyabhicārāddhi sarvam etadavasthitam|| 175.8||
prakāśajananaṃ sattvaṃ rajaḥ saṃgapravartanam|
tamo vimohanaṃ caiva guṇavistara ucyate|| 175.9||
bhinnakāryapracārāṇām eteṣāṃ guṇasaṃjñinām|
hetunā puruṣārthena sādhikā vṛttirucyate|| 175.10|
daivam aṣṭavibhedaṃ tu tiryak saptavidhaṃ smṛtam|
avikalpyaṃ ca mānuṣyaṃ sarvam etadguṇātmakam|| 175.11||
mūḍhaṃ niścetanaṃ bhūtaṃ sthūlaṃ sūkṣmam athāpi vā|
amūrtaṃ mūrtimadvāpi triguṇaṃ sarvam ucyate|| 175.12||
mokṣavighnakarā hyete kīrtitā yogino guṇāḥ|
saktasyaiva hi bandhaḥ syādasakto mukta ucyate|
vibhāgāt prakṛtisthasya sthitā nityaṃ guṇatrayam|| 175.13||
vibhāgena vikārasthā yathādharmaṃ samāśritāḥ|
bhūtasargastridhābhūtaḥ sāṃkhyajñaiḥ paripaṭhyate|| 175.14||
saṃsiddhaḥ prākṛtaścaiva tathā vaikṛta ucyate|
tatra dharmeṇa saṃsiddhā yoge māheśvare sthitāḥ|| 175.15||
necchanti saṃbhavaṃ vyāsa dharmo (?) pañcātmataḥ smṛtaḥ|
te puno dravyasaṃbandhāt sāṃkhyadṛṣṭāntapaṇḍitāḥ|| 175.16||
icchanti kāryam āśritya kāraṇāśrayiṇo na hi|
pradhānāt puruṣādbuddhirabhūt sattvādhikāsakṛt|| 175.17||
guṇānāṃ pariṇāmena prākṛtānāṃ jalādivat|
vyavasāyastathā rūpaṃ niścayaśceti bhāṣyate|| 175.18||
buddhireva hyahaṃkāraḥ pratyayāntarasaṃbhavāt|
manaḥ kecit tam icchanti kriyājaṃ guṇasaṃgraham|| 175.19||
aham eva hi karteti ahaṃkāra udāhṛtaḥ|
manasaḥ kalpanaṃ vāpi smṛtam indriyagocaram|
buddhibhūtādahaṃkārāt sattvotpannāt prakāśinaḥ|| 175.20||
buddhīndriyāṇi jātāni pañca sattvodayāni tu|
bodhyate budhyate vāpi mumukṣustvindriyairyataḥ|| 175.21||
tato buddhīndriyāṇīti kīrtyante tattvacintakaiḥ|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|| 175.22||
ataḥ karmendriyāṇi āhurguṇājjātāni rājasāt|
tāmasādapyahaṃkārāt tanmātrāṇyabhavan punaḥ|| 175.23||
kecit sarvagatāni āhu -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- vidhaṃ tacca dharmādharmasamudbhavam|| 175.24||
yāti sarvatra siddhārthaṃ bhūtavyāpi vimohanam|
śaktaṃ sarvāśrayaṃ sūkṣmam anivāritadikpatham|| 175.25||
liṅgaṃ tacca samākhyātaṃ dehināṃ yacca kāraṇam|
yaśca sargastridhā proktaḥ sa eva navadhā punaḥ|| 175.26||
prākṛtasya vikārasya dehabhedāḥ sahasraśaḥ|
tattvasargaḥ smṛtaḥ pūrvaḥ piṇḍasargastato 'aparaḥ|| 175.27||
pratyayānāṃ tataḥ sargastṛtīyaḥ samudāhṛtaḥ|
asaktirvilayastuṣṭiḥ siddhiśceti catusthi --|| 175.28||
bhedāḥ pratyayasarge tu vaiṣamyādapare smṛtāḥ|
pañcāśat parito bhedā ye ca teṣāṃ guṇā daśa|| 175.29||
ṣaṣṭirete padārthā hi gīyante kapilādibhiḥ|
sā tuṣṭirnavadhā bhinnā siddhiścaivāṣṭadhā punaḥ|| 175.30||
smṛtaḥ pañcavidhaścāpi teṣām eva viparyayaḥ|
aṣṭabhedāstribhinnā syāddaśabhiḥ kāryabandhanaiḥ|| 175.31||
ete ṣaṣṭipadārthāstu saṃkhyājñānam iti śrutiḥ|
nyūnām ekādhikām eke ṣaṣṭim anye tu jānate|| 175.32||
mamaiva hi purā vatsa guṇaje padapañcake|
antaraṃ tattvam anveṣṭuṃ prakṛteḥ puruṣasya ca|| 175.33||
sāṃkhyatantraṃ mahadbuddhvā jñātvā tat prakṛteḥ param|
pañcaviṃśam ajaṃ tattvaṃ bhoktāram abhimāninam|| 175.34||
saṃdehāpagamo nābhūdabuddhvā parameśvaram|
yadāhaṃ devadevena svayam eva jagatsṛjā|| 175.35||
svayogaṃ śambhunā vatsa grāhito gatasaṃśayaḥ|
tadā ṣaḍviṃśakaṃ tattvaṃ jñātvā sarvagam īśvaram|| 175.36||
vimukto yogasaṃsiddhau jāto 'ahaṃ mohavarjitaḥ|
bhoktā cet prakṛterasti bhuṅkte ca puruṣaḥ svayam|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- napi dvija|| 175.37||
yastayoḥ parato nityaḥ ṣaḍviṃśastu īśvaro vibhuḥ|
taṃ jñātvā paramaṃ tattvaṃ mucyate janmabandhanāt|| 175.38||
sāṃkhyaṃ kṛtsnam api jñātvā guṇāntaravicāraṇāt|
pañcaviṃśakasaṃbodhānnaiva muktiḥ prajāyate|
sa baddho bhoktṛpāśaistu guṇaiḥ prakṛtisaṃbhavaiḥ|| 175.39||
abhimānātmako bhoktā puruṣatvādamocakaḥ|
taṃ viditvāpi naiva syānmuktiḥ pratyayavarjitā|| 175.40||
eṣa uktaḥ samāsena sāṃkhyasiddhāntavistaraḥ|
yogatattvaṃ pravakṣyāmi duḥkhajanmavināśanam|| 175.41||
saṃbhavaṃ dehinaścaiva vairāgyaṃ yena codbhavet|
dharmādharmaparityāgaṃ satyānṛtavivarjitam|| 175.42||
yogābhyāsaṃ parāsaṃgaṃ sūkṣmajñānam aninditam|
sarvasaṃsaktinirmuktam īśvaraprāptikāraṇam|| 175.43||
siddhinirdvandvasaṃyogam aśubhodayanāśanam|
paropalabdhivijñānaṃ tattvārthapadaniścayam|| 175.44||
bhavajanmāpahaṃ yogaṃ viṣayendriyavarjitam|
mataṃ paśupateḥ kṛtsnam amṛtāspadalambhanam|| 175.45||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane dhyānavidhau
dvitīyo 'ayaṃ pañcasaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 175.175||

ṣaṭsaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
utpadyate yathā janturvairāgyaṃ vrajate yathā|
yathā prabudhyate caiva tat te vyāsa vadāmyaham|| 176.1||
ākāśaḥ pavanastejo bhūmirāpastathaiva ca|
eṣām ekatra saṃghātāccharīraṃ nāma jāyate|| 176.2||
rasāḥ somātmakāḥ sarve tathāhāraścaturvidhaḥ|
dehināṃ tu rasotpattirāhārasya niṣevaṇāt|| 176.3||
rasādraktasamutpattiḥ śoṇitāt piśitaṃ smṛtam|
meda utpadyate māṃsāt tasmādasthīni cābhavan|| 176.4||
majjā cāsthibhavā jñeyā tataḥ śukrasamudbhavaḥ|
raktaśukrasamāyogādgarbhaḥ saṃbhavati striyāḥ|| 176.5||
ṛtuyogasamādhānāddaivakarmavaśādapi|
striyāḥ puṃsaśca ratyante dvāvapyekatvam āgatau|| 176.6||
tāvekatvam athāpannau preritau pavanena ca|
kalalaṃ tvekarātreṇa pañcarātreṇa cārbudam|| 176.7||
piśitaṃ saptarātreṇa māsāccāṅkurasaṃbhavaḥ|
tataḥprabhṛti garbhasya vibhāgo bhavati dvija|| 176.8||
śiraḥpāṇimukhaskandhagrīvāpṛṣṭhādisaṃyutaḥ|
pañcānām atha māsānām akṣikarṇādisaṃbhavaḥ|| 176.9||
sarvasaṃpūrṇagātrastu srotobhirnavabhiryutaḥ|
vyaktībhavati tadgarbho māsairaṣṭabhireva tu|| 176.10||
saṃprāpte navame māsi sarvadravyasamanvitaḥ|
pañcabhūtātmakaṃ tat tu cetovadavatiṣṭhati|| 176.11||
garbhakledena siktāṅgaḥ sarvaduḥkhasamanvitaḥ|
jātiṃ smaredvasaṃstatra jantuḥ sarvasamudbhavām|| 176.12||
mṛtaḥ puno 'ahaṃ jāto jātaścaiva puno mṛtaḥ|
idānīṃ jātamātrastu yogam evābhyāsāmyaham|| 176.13||
na puno yena saṃsāraṃ pravekṣyāmyaśubhodayam|
evaṃ cintayatastasya navame māsi saṃgate|| 176.14||
svakarmavinibaddhasya jātamātrasya dehinaḥ|
deham āviśate vāyuḥ smṛtim ākṣipya tāmasaḥ|| 176.15||
yena mūḍho nirānando naivādhyātmaratirbhavet|
agnīṣomātmakaṃ sarvaṃ bhūtagrāmaṃ caturvidham|| 176.16||
saṃyogādevam utpannam utpatsyati ca suvrata|
tatra ye sādhusaṃparkācchubhakarmodayādapi|| 176.17||
āgamānveṣaṇe saktāḥ pāpānuṣṭhānavarjitāḥ|
matvā saṃsārajaṃ kleśaṃ janmamṛtyubhayārditam|| 176.18||
kāmakrodharatidrohalobhamohasamāvṛtam|
vairāgyaṃ janmataḥ kṛtvā sarvārambhaparikṣayāt|| 176.19||
anviṣanti śubhārthaṃ hi guhyam adhyātmadarśanam|
te yogaṃ paramaṃ prāpya brahma vindanti tat param|| 176.20||
tasya te saṃpravakṣyāmi brahmasaṃbodhakāraṇam|
sarveṣāṃ yogināṃ guhyaṃ sarvayoganidarśanam|| 176.21||
tato māheśvaraṃ yogam ākhyāsye tat paraṃ tava|
tejāgniḥ kāmajo vahniḥ krodhāgnirvīkṣaṇānalaḥ|| 176.22||
jaṭharāgniśca bhūtātmā pañcaite dehavahnayaḥ|
prāṇo 'apānaḥ samānaśca udāno vyāna eva ca|| 176.23||
pañcaite vāyavo nityā dehino dehasaṃbhavāḥ|
ākāśaprabhavā hyete śarīraṃ caiṣu tiṣṭhati|| 176.24||
māṃsaraktasamākīrṇaṃ snāyumedosthisaṃcayam|
tvacāvanaddhaṃ durgandhaṃ śakṛnmūtrasamāvṛtam|| 176.25||
taḍidabhrāgamānityaṃ mṛtpātrāpātasaṃnibham|
sarvānarthasamāyuktaṃ na cirānnāśagāmi ca|| 176.26||
ekarūpaṃ navadvāraṃ tristhūṇaṃ pañcadevatam|
viṣayendriyasaṃkīrṇaṃ naikavyādhisamārditam|| 176.27||
prāṇādibhiravaṣṭabdhaṃ śarīraṃ yantravat sthitam|
vimuktam asakṛt taistu vāyubhirjīvasaṃhataiḥ|| 176.28||
āmapātram ivāpātācchīryate kālaparyayāt|
pañcabhūtāni bhūtāni dehānniṣkramya sarvaśaḥ|| 176.29||
āviśanti tathātmānam ātmā ca viśate drutam|
bhūteṣu pavanaḥ śreṣṭho jīvastadvinibandhanaḥ|| 176.30||
vāyvagnī sahitau jīvo na jīvaḥ prāṇināṃ pṛthak|
mūrtiranyā na jīvasya mṛtyau dṛśyati dehinaḥ|| 176.31||
pañcarūpāt paro devaḥ sūkṣmāt sūkṣmataro mataḥ|
nāsau paśyati na ghrāti na śṛṇoti na jalpati|| 176.32||
na jānāti na ca sparśejjīvaḥ prāṇasamāvṛtaḥ|
prāṇo nāma mahāvāyurjīvaṃ dhārayate dvija|| 176.33||
bhāsate śvasate caiva sarveṣvapi hi dehiṣu|
sa prāṇo dhārayatyagniṃ sa ca jīva iti smṛtaḥ|| 176.34||
vāyusaṃdhāraṇo hyagniḥ kriyāsu parivartate|
yo vahnimānasau dehe sa jīva iti śabdyate|| 176.35||
antargato hi bhūtānāṃ karmārambhanibandhanaḥ|
evam etaccharīraṃ tu pañcabhūtaguṇātmakam|| 176.36||
tadvikāre pranaṣṭe tu mṛta ityabhidhīyate|
bhūtendriyamanojīvaviṣayā rāgabandhane|| 176.37||
hṛdaye karṇikāyāṃ tu madhyasthastejasāṃ nidhiḥ|
ātmā sarvagato nityaṃ varjito viṣayādibhiḥ|| 176.38||
tiṣṭhate sa vibhustatra yaṃ viditvā vimucyate|
sa yena yogasaṃsiddhyā dhyānakarmakriyāvidā|| 176.39||
nāḍīkarmasamādhānāt satatābhyāsayogataḥ|
bhābhiḥ prakāśito dṛṣṭo vikārairvipramocitaḥ|| 176.40||
dṛṣṭo bhavati viprendra muktiścaiva tataḥ smṛtā|
ṣaḍviṃśakaparijñānāllayam ādhāya tatra hi|| 176.41||
sarvaprāṇigataṃ sūkṣmam ātmadehe ca saṃsthitam|
yaṃ prapaśyanti saṃsiddhā yogino gatabandhanāḥ|| 176.42||
yo 'abhyupāyaḥ parastasya vijñānād īśvarasya tu|
yogābhyāsaṃ paraṃ taṃ te pravakṣyāmi dvijottama|| 176.43||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane dhyānavidhau
tṛtīyaḥ ṣaṭsaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 176.176||

saptasaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
antarātmā ca cetovān manaḥ saṃkalpajaṃ smṛtam|
mahābhūtapracārācca kṣobhāgnirjīva ucyate|| 177.1||
na śarīraṃ vinā cetastaccennāsti kutaśca tat|
ceto 'api na vinā jīvaṃ sa cāpi na vinā manaḥ|| 177.2||
prāṇo jīva iti proktaḥ sparśādanyat pravartate|
manaḥ sarvaṃ nibadhnāti karmārambham iti śrutiḥ|| 177.3||
sarva ete hi saṃgatya dhārayanti śarīriṇam|
yasya ceto 'adhikaṃ teṣāṃ sa cetovān prakīrtitaḥ|| 177.4||
cetasā tu vijānāti śubhāśubhanibandhanam|
tanmanaścetasi sthāpya nityādhyātmaratirbhavet|| 177.5||
śabdādiviṣayātīta indriyāṇi nigṛhya tu|
dhyānārambhaparo dehī sa syāt karmavivarjitaḥ|| 177.6||
indriyāṇi na badhnanti mano dehasamāsthitam|
jīvo bandhātmako jñeyaḥ śubhāśubhanibandhanāt|| 177.7||
rajasastamasaścaiva guṇayoraśubhātmanoḥ|
udrekājjāyate duḥkhaṃ saukhyaṃ sattvāt prajāyate|| 177.8||
saukhyasya pariṇāmāddhi duḥkhotpattiḥ śarīriṇām|
jāyate ca sukhaṃ vipra bhūyo duḥkhaparyayāt|| 177.9||
evam anyonyasaṃbaddhaṃ guṇatrayavikārajaṃ|
sukhaduḥkhātmakaṃ mohaṃ bhūtāni āviśya tiṣṭhati|| 177.10||
manaścetaḥsamādhānādviṣayodvijanādapi|
tasya nāśaḥ samākhyātaḥ saṃgasya ca vivarjanāt|| 177.11||
icchānigrahaṇe saktāḥ krodhādiparivarjitāḥ|
nirmamā nirahaṃkārā badhyante naiva karmabhiḥ|| 177.12||
ātmā sarvagato hyeṣaḥ sūkṣmaḥ saṃbhogavarjitaḥ|
yoginastaṃ prapaśyanti dhyānādvāyuvivarjanāt|| 177.13||
tāvadbhramati saṃsāre caturyoniṣu jantuṣu|
yāvannātmānam anveṣṭi sa ca vinno na janma ca|| 177.14||
yadyapi dhyānasaṃsargādabuddhvā brahma naśyati|
tathāpi brahmasāyujyānna tu janma puno labhet|| 177.15||
athaiśvaryaṃ paraṃ dhyānādyogajaṃ prāpnute muniḥ|
viditvā paramātmānaṃ tato na puna āvrajet|| 177.16||
asukhānyapi karmāṇi mahāpāpakṛtānyapi|
kṛtvā dhyānarato jantustarasā nayati kṣayam|| 177.17||
prāpya karmakṣayaṃ kṛtsnaṃ dhyānayuktyā mahāmune|
tiṣṭhate nirbhayo yogī paramaiśvaryasaṃyutaḥ|| 177.18||
kāmaroṣau tathā saṃgo dveṣo rāgaviniścayaḥ|
ete kṣudratarā bhāvā mukta ebhirvimucyate|| 177.19||
garvo dambho hyahaṃkārastarko māno 'atha matsaraḥ|
pāruṣyaṃ krūratā caiva bhāvāḥ kṣatranibandhanāḥ|| 177.20||
yasyaite mohanā na syurvindanti ātmānam īśvaram|
mohabhāvāntarātītaḥ samaduḥkhasukhaḥ sadā|| 177.21||
nirmamatvādibhiryukto yogīti paripaṭhyate|
yajñakarma samutsṛjya vaiṣṇavaṃ mohabandhanam|| 177.22||
adhyātmaparamo nityaṃ mumukṣurbrāhmaṇo bhavet|
trivargaṃ saṃparityajya yogavarge ratiṃ labhet|| 177.23||
divaukasām asau pūjyo vipra ityabhidhīyate|
dhyānena kṣīyate karma pāpaṃ vā yadi vā śubham|| 177.24||
kṣīṇakarmā tato yogī tat paraṃ brahma vindati|
prāptayogo munirdhyānī yadyat kartum abhīpsate|| 177.25||
tat tadbhavati tasyāśu manasā cintitena vā|
yoginaṃ puruṣaṃ dṛṣṭvā pāpairmucyanti tatkṣaṇāt|
yo 'api saṃbhāṣate tena so 'api sadgatim āpnute|| 177.26||
yogam eva paraṃ jñātvā sarvāśubhavimocanam|
sacetaso dvijā vipra babhūvurhi mumukṣavaḥ|| 177.27||
dhyānaṃ dhyeyaṃ paraṃ caiva dhātāraṃ caiva ye viduḥ|
tāpanāt tapanāt tāpyānmuktāste duḥkhabandhanāt|| 177.28||
sarvārambhaparityāgānmamatvādivivarjanāt|
sāṃkhyayogāgamāvekau bhedastattvavimocane|| 177.29||
nirguṇaḥ sāṃkhyamukhyānāṃ puruṣaḥ paripaṭhyate|
dīpanirvāṇavat teṣāṃ dehabhede gatiḥ smṛtā|| 177.30||
īśvaraḥ sarvanirmuktaḥ kṣetrajño yogināṃ mataḥ|
paramaiśvaryasaṃyuktāstaṃ viśanti hi yoginaḥ|| 177.31||
dhāraṇābhiḥ samaṃ tābhiḥ prāṇāyāmaistathaiva ca|
ātmānaṃ yojayedyastu sa yogaṃ labhate param|| 177.32||
ahiṃsādisamāyukto yogī vigatamatsaraḥ|
dhyānam abhyasate yastu sa jayenmṛtyujanmanī|| 177.33||
nirguṇo nirahaṃkāro jitadvandvo 'anavagrahaḥ|
bhikṣopāttarasāhāro mumukṣuriti śabdyate|| 177.34||
sarvārambhasamāvasthaḥ sarvāśrayavivarjitaḥ|
karmamārgādatikrānto dhyānīti parikīrtyate|| 177.35||
yasya nodvijate ceto duḥkhāpattau mahāmune|
na hṛṣyati sukhe caiva dhyānīti sa viśabditaḥ|| 177.36||
mokṣasiddhipradaḥ panthāstrividhaḥ parikīrtitaḥ|
pūrvaḥ saṃketanaḥ proktaḥ paścāt saṃkathanaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 177.37||
saṃsaktaśca tṛtīyastu teṣāṃ bhedam imaṃ śṛṇu|
pratirūpaṃ vibhoḥ kṛtvā daśabhirniyamairyutaḥ|| 177.38||
upāste yo munirdhyāyan sa saṃketana ucyate|
vedādṛtasukhāsaṃgaḥ sattvakarmā tvabāndhavān|| 177.39||
parityajyeśvaraṃ dhyāyet tat saṃkathanam ucyate|
sarvārambhaparityāgāt kapilādiniṣevitaḥ|| 177.40||
smṛtaḥ saṃkathanaḥ panthā yogāgniparidīpakaḥ|
nirvikalpastu yaḥ sarvaṃ brahma eveti paśyati|| 177.41||
bhinnasarvakriyācāro dhyānī saṃsakta ucyate|
trividhasyāpi mārgasya niyamāniyamāni ca|| 177.42||
tānyeva parikīrtyante caryābhedāstvanekadhā|
trayo 'api hetavo mukterime dhyānapathā mune|| 177.43||
samyagetān munirjñātvā nirmamo 'anyatamaṃ śritaḥ|
tadāpnoti paraṃ dhyānaṃ yena vindati tat param|| 177.44||
sarvān dhyānavidhāṃstvetānucyamānānimān mayā|
śṛṇu vyāsa mahābuddhe yogaiśvaryaphalapradān|| 177.45||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane dhyānavidhau
caturthaḥ saptasaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 177.177||

saptasaptatyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
dvividhaṃ brahma nirdiṣṭaṃ kṣaram akṣaram eva ca|
viditvobhayam etaddhi mucyate sarvabandhanaiḥ|| 178.1||
pañcaviṃśatimaṃ tattvaṃ kṣaraṃ tat prakṛteḥ param|
akṣaraṃ ca paraṃ brahma ṣaḍviṃśakam iti smṛtam|| 178.2||
mana ekagataṃ kṛtvā dhāraṇābhiḥ punaḥ punaḥ|
vāyunigrahaṇaṃ kuryāt pratyāhārapuraḥsaram|| 178.3||
muhūrtārdhaṃ kṣaṇaṃ vāpi pratyāhāraṃ samācaret|
talāt triṃśacchataṃ cordhvaṃ prāṇāyāmanibandhanam|| 178.4||
abhyastamānasaṃ yat syāt svastikādi prakīrtitam|
tadbaddhvā vijane deśe dhyānābhyāsaṃ samācaret|| 178.5||
kṣudhārto vātibhukto vā rujā duḥkhānvito 'api vā|
na dhyāyīta puno vidvān ya iccheddhyānam ātmanaḥ|| 178.6||
yogahastaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā vāmasyopari dakṣiṇam|
adhomukho bhavet kiṃcit paśyan nāsāgram ātmanaḥ|| 178.7||
aspṛśan daśanairdantānoṃkāraṃ brahma saṃsmaran|
dhyāyīta nirmamo vidvān prāṇāyāmapuraḥsaram|| 178.8||
ātmānam ātmanā yojya sarvāṅgāni tu saṃharet|
nirīhaḥ pihitākṣaśca nikṣipya hṛdi dhāraṇām|| 178.9||
pāṣāṇa iva niṣpando munirdhyānaṃ samācaret|
ekatrāspandasaṃdhānaṃ manaso dhāraṇā smṛtā|| 178.10||
evaṃ pratidinaṃ tasya dhyāyato yogino mune|
vikārā guṇajāḥ sarve naśyante vighnahetavaḥ|| 178.11||
anveṣṭi ca paraṃ brahma svaśarīraṃ samāsthitam|
kṛtvaikyaṃ prāṇamanasām indriyāṇāṃ vinigrahāt|| 178.12||
sarvabhāvaparityāgānmokṣam āpnotyasaṃśayam|
pratyāhārarataṃ kṛtvā sarvam indriyagocaram|| 178.13||
tato yuñjīta nirdvandvo manaḥsaṃdhānam ācaran|
sarvaṃ manasi saṃsthāpya paraṃ tattvaṃ nirūpayet|| 178.14||
athaiśvaryagatāṃ siddhiṃ dhyāyannaṣṭavidhāṃ yadā|
paśyate yogasaṃsiddhyā tadā yogī prakīrtyate|| 178.15||
brahmasomādikān devān yadā yuktaḥ prapaśyati|
yogibhiḥ kathyate hyeṣā siddhiryogavikārajā|| 178.16||
manasā yogināṃ siddhiḥ sāṃkhyāstattvaviniścayāt|
na viśeṣo 'asti yogānāṃ muktvā māheśvaraṃ vidhim|| 178.17||
yogino dhyānasaṃsiddhiṃ sāṃkhyāstattvaviniścayam|
avibhinnāvubhāvetau dhyānatattvārthaniścayau|| 178.18||
sarvabandhaparibhraṣṭaḥ saṃgadoṣavivarjitaḥ|
rāgamohādisaṃtyakto mukta ityabhidhīyate|| 178.19||
śabdādīn viṣayān yukto na dhyāyan vetti vai yadā|
asakṛdyogasaṃsiddhyā tadā paśyati tat param|| 178.20||
mṛtyujanmabhayodvignaḥ saṃgadoṣavivarjitaḥ|
araṇye maunam ādhāya dhyāyedoṃkāram akṣaram|| 178.21||
vedādau yaḥ svaraḥ prokto vedānte ca pratiṣṭhitaḥ|
tasya prakṛtilīnasya yaḥ paraḥ sa mahān smṛtaḥ|| 178.22||
trisaṃsthānaṃ trimātraṃ ca tribrahma tryakṣaraṃ tathā|
mātrāhīnaṃ samātraṃ ca yo vidyāt sa vimucyate|| 178.23||
nāgnistatra na vāyuśca na somo na divākaraḥ|
prabhavanti maheśāne īśvare trivikalpite|| 178.24||
oṃkāraḥ paramaṃ tattvam ātmā brahma ca kīrtyate|
kṣetrajñairātmasaṃbodhādyogibhiḥ sūkṣmadarśanāt|| 178.25||
evam eva sadā dhyāyan mana ātmani yojayet|
īśvaraṃ prāpnute yogī yam avāpya vimucyate|| 178.26||
indriyāṇi tu sarvāṇi śabdarūpādinigrahāt|
viditvā karmajān hanti yogī doṣānaśeṣataḥ|| 178.27||
dhyānaśaktyā tataḥ śuddhaḥ sarvajinmokṣam āpnute|
yuñjan pratidinaṃ vyāsa ṣaṅmāsādyogam āpnute|| 178.28||
paśyate ca paraṃ brahma yena mucyeta bandhanāt|
tam ātmānaṃ paraṃ jñātvā yogaśaktyā mahāmuniḥ|
paramaiśvaryasaṃyukta amṛtaṃ padam āpnuyāt|| 178.29||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane dhyānavidhau
pañcamaḥ aṣṭasaptatyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 178.178||

ūnāśītyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
antaḥkaraṇasaṃsiddho yo mahān kathito mayā|
pañca karmendriyāṇyatra pañca buddhīndriyāṇi ca|| 179.1||
pañcabhūtaṃ manaścātra vikārāḥ ṣoḍaśa smṛtāḥ|
mahān buddhirahaṃkārastanmātrāṇi ca pañca hi|| 179.2||
imāḥ prakṛtayo vyāsa deham aṣṭau samāśritāḥ|
tattvāni tu caturviṃśatyetānyuktāni yogibhiḥ|
deham ebhiravaṣṭabdhaṃ trailokyavyāpibhiḥ sthitam|| 179.3||
nābhimadhye tu nāḍīnāṃ śatam ekaṃ pratiṣṭhitam|
sarvāṅgeṣu tu yāstvanyā jalānnarasavāhikāḥ|| 179.4||
tāsāṃ triṃśat sahasrāṇi vyānasrotasi saṃsthitāḥ|
udānasyāparā nāḍyo brahmamūrdhni pratiṣṭhitāḥ|| 179.5||
cakranābhī samāśritya bhūtasaṃghātam āsthitam|
tanmadhye tu guṇaspṛṣṭaḥ karmātmā bhūtamohanaḥ|| 179.6||
nakṣatroddyotasaṃkāśo jyotsnāpuñjanibhaḥ prabhaḥ|
vighātajanano 'anyeṣāṃ sūryāyutanibhaḥ sthitaḥ|| 179.7||
saṃbhūto 'agnirivotpātī girinīhārasaṃnibhaḥ|
guṇastho bhūtayonistu puruṣaḥ pañcaviṃśakaḥ|| 179.8||
tasyāpi parataḥ śuddho mahānagnirivotthitaḥ|
arciṣmān sarvato dīpto nirvikalpo nirañjanaḥ|| 179.9||
nirdhūmāṅgārasaṃkāśo navijñātāgamakriyaḥ|
ṣaḍviṃśaḥ puruṣaḥ sūkṣma īśvaraḥ paramo vibhuḥ|| 179.10||
sa eṣa kathito vyāsa pareṣāṃ parataḥ sthitaḥ|
mahādevam imaṃ jñātvā mucyate tatkṣaṇānmuniḥ|| 179.11||
guṇatrayavikārasthaḥ kathitaḥ pañcaviṃśakaḥ|
bhūyaḥ saṃsarate tasmādajñānenaiva mohitaḥ|| 179.12||
devamānuṣatiryakṣu bhrāmyate rāgamohitaḥ|
ṣaḍviṃśakasamādhānāt siddhistasya vikārataḥ|| 179.13||
kriyākāryavinirmuktaḥ sarvajñaḥ sarvasṛk prabhuḥ|
paramaiśvaryasaṃpūrṇaḥ kṛtakṛtyo maheśvaraḥ|| 179.14||
ajaḥ svayambhūḥ ṣaḍviṃśaḥ kūṭastho hyacalo dhruvaḥ|
tatastattvāni jāyante puruṣaśca guṇaiḥ saha|| 179.15||
tasminneva ca līyante ṣaḍviṃśe tu maheśvare|
viditvainaṃ maheśānaṃ muktisiddhiravāpyate|| 179.16||
etajjñātvā na lipyeta karmabhirmohabandhanaiḥ|
yathāgnirnirdahedante bhūtagrāmam aśeṣataḥ|| 179.17||
ṣaḍviṃśakapadārthajñastathā karmāṇi nirdahet|
sarvavyāpi yathākāśaṃ sūkṣmaṃ naiva tu lipyate|| 179.18||
ṣaḍviṃśakarato yogī tathā pāpairna lipyate|
ṣaḍviṃśāt parato nāsti tasmāt tatparamo bhavet|| 179.19||
ekatvaṃ saha tenaiva tyaktvā deham avāpnute|
brahmaviṣṇvādikaṃ sarvaṃ bhūtagrāmam aśeṣataḥ|| 179.20||
īśvarājjāyate vyāsa tasminneva pralīyate|
nāsti tasmāt paro hyanyastaṃ vidyāt sarvataḥ sthitam|| 179.21||
yam adhyātmavidaḥ siddhāḥ paramātmetyupāsate|
sa eṣa sarvago devaḥ ṣaḍviṃśaḥ parameśvaraḥ|| 179.22||
prāṇo 'apānaḥ samānaśca udāno vyāna eva ca|
ye pañca vāyavo dehe teṣāṃ nigrahaṇe yatet|| 179.23||
apānaṃ ca samāṇaṃ ca kṛtvaikagatam ādṛtaḥ|
vyānena sahitaṃ prāṇam udāne saṃniveśayet|| 179.24||
nāsāgre tu sakṛt prāṇaṃ prāpayedyogaśaktitaḥ|
bhadrāṃ dṛṣṭiṃ samāsthāya ṣaḍviṃśaṃ cintayet tataḥ|| 179.25||
mātrāḥ pañcadaśa proktāḥ prathamaṃ sandhibandhanam|
mātrā viṃśati vijñeyāḥ pañcamaḥ sandhivigrahaḥ|| 179.26||
niḥśabde vijane deśe nirīho vijitendriyaḥ|
svastikaṃ padmakaṃ bhadram athavā siṃhakacchapau|| 179.27||
ekam āsanam āsthāya ṣaḍviṃśaṃ samanusmaran|
sarvāṅgāni samāhṛtya niṣpando dhyānam ācaret|| 179.28||
śanaiḥ saṃcārayedvāyuṃ nāḍibhiḥ srotasi sthitam|
tāvat tiṣṭheta yuktātmā dhyānayogādgataspṛhaḥ|| 179.29||
somamaṇḍalasaṃkāśaṃ yāvat paśyeddhṛdi sthitam|
jyotirdehāśritaṃ dṛṣṭvā yogaiśvaryaṃ pravartate|| 179.30||
tata evaṃ sadābhyāsādyogasiddhipravartanāt|
trikālaviṣayaṃ jñānaṃ pratyakṣaṃ yogino bhavet|| 179.31||
vyādhyayo nāviśantyenaṃ na ca duḥkhānvito bhavet|
svadehasya ca saugandhyaṃ vapurdivyaṃ ca jāyate|| 179.32||
amoghaṃ ca vacastasya śāpānugrahakāritam|
pratyavāyo na caivāsya bhavet karmanibandhanaḥ|| 179.33||
sarvavidyāvidāṃ vyāsa yatīnāṃ vratacāriṇām|
tapasvināṃ ca viprāṇāṃ yogī śreṣṭha udāhṛtaḥ|| 179.34||
nānyathā mucyate jantuḥ saṃsārāt tamasaḥ parāt|
ṣaḍviṃśakaparijñānaṃ muktvā yoganibandhanam|| 179.35||
ṣaḍaṅgena tu yogena tathā pañcavidhena ca|
jitvā hyaṣṭaprakāraṃ tu āsanānāṃ nibandhanam|| 179.36||
mātrotkarṣeṇa jitvā ca prāṇāyāmaṃ caturvidham|
tanmātrāṇīndriyairjitvā viṣayairindriyāṇi ca||| 179.37||
ahaṃkārabhayāyāsakrodhalobhavivarjitaḥ|
vimatsaro 'atha niḥsaṃgo niḥsneho niḥspṛhastathā|| 179.38||
yogāspadaṃ samādhāya pūrvoktaṃ guṇavarjitam|
dhyāyīta hṛdi taṃ devaṃ viśvaṃ viśveśvaraṃ vibhum|| 179.39||
anādinidhanaṃ śāntaṃ traiguṇyaparivarjitam|
tālau jihvāṃ samādhāya dantairdantān na ca spṛśan|| 179.40||
indriyāṇi manaścaiva paramātmani yojayet|
kṛtvā manasi tat sarvaṃ prāṇāpānau niruddhya ca|| 179.41||
oṃkāraṃ tvasakṛddhyāyan saṃhṛtyāṅgāni kūrmavat|
śarīraṃ sarvam āpūrya vikṣipet sarvam ātmani|| 179.42||
tat saṃhṛtya munirbhūyo vyāpi bhūtaṃ pravistṛtam|
nāḍīvāyupracāreṇa bhūyo bhūyastathārabhet|| 179.43||
sa pūrvāpararātre tu sāttvikaṃ ceta ucyate|
madhyāṅge cāparāhaṇe ca kṛṣṇaṃ dhyāyīta tāmasam|| 179.44||
sandhyayorubhayornityaṃ rājasaṃ dhyānam ācaret|
taijasaṃ sarvataścāpi dhyānadevaṃ jayedguṇān|| 179.45||
sadaivaṃ dhyayato vyāsa tadaiśvaryaṃ pravartate|
yena ṣaḍviṃśakaṃ buddhvā hṛdayasthaṃ maheśvaram|| 179.46||
svecchayā svatanuṃ tyaktvā tasminneva pralīyate|
paramātmā paraṃ brahma kāraṇaṃ puruṣo mahān|| 179.47||
īśvaro nirguṇo bhoktā ṣaḍviṃśaḥ samudāhṛtaḥ|
yaccāsat sadasaccaiva bhūtibhūto vibhuḥ paraḥ|| 179.48||
jāgarti svapate bhuṅkte saṃtiṣṭhati dadāti ca|
sa sraṣṭā sa ca saṃhartā guṇātīto maheśvaraḥ|| 179.49||
ityetat kathitaṃ sarvaṃ sarvayoganidarśanam|
yogaṃ pāśupataṃ tubhyam ādyaṃ mokṣagatipradam|| 179.50||
sarvaprasaṅgarahitaṃ haravaktraviniḥsṛtam|
sūkṣmaṃ tat paramaṃ jñānaṃ pravakṣyāmi tavānagha|
yasya samyakparijñānādvijñeyaṃ nāparaṃ bhavet|| 179.51||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane dhyānavidhau
ṣaṣṭha ūnāśītyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 179.179||

aśītyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
brahmādyā devatā vyāsa dakṣayajñavadhe purā|
śaṃkaraṃ śaraṇaṃ jagmurvīrabhadrabhayārditāḥ|| 180.1||
gaṇendreṇābhiyuktāstu bhasmakūṭāni bhejire|
yadā bhasma praviṣṭāste tejaḥ śāṃkaram uttamam|| 180.2||
abhavaṃste tadā raudrāḥ paśavo dīkṣitā iva|
bhasmābhasitagātrāṇāṃ śaṃkaravratacāriṇām|| 180.3||
svaṃ yogaṃ pradadau teṣāṃ tadā deva umāpatiḥ|
sarvāsāṃ mokṣavidyānāṃ yat tattvam atiricyate|| 180.4||
hiraṇyagarbhapramukhairyogimukhyaiḥ pravartitaḥ|
yo yogaḥ sakalo vyāsa kṛcchropāyaprasādhanaḥ|| 180.5||
janmāntarasahasraistu tam abhyasya mahāmune|
prāpnuvanti paraṃ jyotiryogaiśvaryam athāpi vā|
yo 'ayaṃ bhagavatā sākṣādyogo māheśvaraḥ paraḥ|| 180.6||
tattvataḥ kalpitasteṣāṃ prapannānāṃ divaukasām|
asya samyak parijñānādanenaiva tu janmanā|| 180.7||
vrataṃ pāśupataṃ prāpya ṣaḍmāsājjñānam āpnute|
yogaiśvaryaṃ mahadvyāsa yadavāpya vimucyate|| 180.8||
sarvadharmaṃ bahiḥkṛtvā niṣakalasya prabhāvataḥ|
dīkṣāṃ pāśupatīṃ prāpya taṃ viśanti maheśvaram|| 180.9||
sarvajñānasamāyuktaṃ tapodharmabahiṣkṛtam|
bhasmasādhanamātraṃ tu śivena kathitaṃ vratam|| 180.10||
pāpiṣṭhā dharmavanto vā bhaktāḥ kevalam īśvaram|
sevanādyasya mucyante tannibodha mahāvratam|| 180.11||
adharmaṃ na vinā dharmo na ca dharmaṃ vināśubham|
etau parasparaṃ baddhau tyaktvā tasmādimāvubhau|| 180.12||
dharmādharmaparityaktaścaret pāśupataṃ vratam|
tato yogam imaṃ prāpya mahadaiśvaryam āpnute|| 180.13||
bhasmagrahaṇamātrāt tu sarvabandhapramocanam|
mucyate spṛṣṭamātrastu brahmapūtena bhasmana|| 180.14||
dahet somakṛtaṃ vahnirīśvaraṃ cānalaṃ viduḥ|
kṛtākṛtaṃ dahatyagnirbhūyaḥ somasamāgataḥ|| 180.15||
bhasmanā mocitāḥ sarve brahmādyā abhimāninaḥ|
bhasmanastejaso vīryaṃ bhasma pāvanam īśvaram|| 180.16||
ātmānam uddharedvyāsa yaḥ snānaṃ bhasmanā caret|
bhasmanā śivayogena mucyate pāśabandhanāt|| 180.17||
prabhavanti surāḥ somāt pitaro vahnisambhavāḥ|
vahnisomātmakaṃ tasmājjagat sarvaṃ pratiṣṭhitam|| 180.18||
īśvaro 'agniśca somaśca bhasma tatteja ucyate|
tejasā tasya saṃspṛṣṭo mucyate janmanā dvijaḥ|| 180.19||
sāṃkhyaṃ visyāstapaścaiva tyaktvā dharmāṃśca vaidikān|
kevalaṃ bhasmasaṃsnānāt pūto gacchati tatpadam|| 180.20||
viṣayānapi saṃsevya bahvadharmarato 'api san|
paścādbhaktiparaḥ śambhorbhasmanaiva hi śuddhyati|| 180.21||
ātmānaṃ yaḥ paśuṃ kṛtvā mahādevaṃ hutāśanam|
dīkṣito brahmabhasmabhyāṃ śivayājī munirbhavet|| 180.22||
śīghram eva paraṃ yogaṃ prāpya mucyeta bandhanāt|
evaṃ vratam anuprāpya bhūtvā pāśupato muniḥ|| 180.23||
idaṃ māheśvaraṃ jñānaṃ guhyaṃ paramam abhyaset|
jñeyaṃ jñānaṃ tathā jñātā trayaṃ dehe yathā sthitam|| 180.24||
ātmā yaśca yathā cāsau sthānatrayasamāsthitaḥ|
nāḍīṣu ca yathā hi ātmā ātmanyevānutiṣṭhati|| 180.25||
sarvataḥ sarvabhūteṣu nigūḍhastiṣṭhate yathā|
payasīva ghṛtaṃ vyāsa yaṃ viditvā vimucyate|| 180.26||
na sa vettuṃ vinā jñānaṃ śakya ātmā kathaṃcana|
rūpaśabdarasātītaṃ kastvaṃ vetti maheśvaram|| 180.27||
tathā hyahaṃ mahābhāga prāsādāt tryambakasya tu|
ātmajñānaṣaropāyaṃ kathayāmi tavānagha|| 180.28||
sarvam eva tamaḥ pūrvam idam āsījjagat kila|
na devā nānilo na dyaurna sūryaścandramā na ca|| 180.29||
na kiṃcit sarvathā bhūtaṃ dṛśyate jagati sthitam|
śuddhaṃ vimalam ābhāti akṣaraṃ paramaiśvaram|| 180.30||
sarvabhāvaguṇātītaṃ nirvikalpaṃ nirañjanam|
bahirantaścaraṃ dīptam avināśi varaṃ dhruvam|
yathā tadakṣaraṃ brahma procyamānaṃ tathā śṛṇu|| 180.31||
om ityeksākṣaraṃ pūrvaṃ kṣaraṃ tasmādvinirgatam|
tryakṣaraśca trimātraśca oṃkāro brahma śabdyate|| 180.32||
akāre tatra viṣṇustu ukāre tu pitāmahaḥ|
makāre bhagavān īśo mātrāyāṃ prakṛtiḥ smṛtā|| 180.33||
brahmaviṣṇū smṛtau yau tau devau īśvaranirgatau|
prakṛtistrītvam āsthāya nityaṃ tau īśapārśvagau|| 180.34||
patnīrūpeṇa sā śambhuṃ bhajate prakṛtiḥ sadā|
kṣaranṃ tu prakṛtiḥ khyātākṣarastu svayam īśvaraḥ|| 180.35||
īśvarānnirgatā sā hi prakṛtirguṇabandhanā|
tasyāḥ sraṣṭā mahādevo yato viṣṇupitāmahau|| 180.36||
prajāpatī samutpannau guṇatrayanibandhanau|
tau ākramya maheśastu prakṛtisthau guṇātmakau|| 180.37||
makārastho vibhurbhūtvā bhuṅkte saṃcarate ca hi|
guhyam etat paraṃ jñātvā mayoktaṃ tattvam akṣaram|| 180.38||
yenaiva dhyāninā vyāsa īśvaro 'asau vikalpitaḥ|
sa tam āviśya muktātmā kṛtārtho jāyate muniḥ|| 180.39||
nainaṃ jānantyamārgasthāstarkahetuparāyaṇāḥ|
bhoktāraṃ prakṛterīśaṃ paraṃ ṣaḍviṃśasaṃjñitam|| 180.40||
oṃkāraḥ prakṛtirnityaṃ tanmadhye ceśvaraḥ sthitaḥ|
payomadhye yathā vyāsa sarpirantargataṃ sthitam|| 180.41||
oṃkāraṃ dhyāyatā yena atītya prakṛtiṃ mune|
īśvaro 'asau mahān vinnaḥ sa muktaḥ paśubandhanaiḥ|| 180.42||
īśvarī prakṛtiḥ khyātā guṇabandhādvimohanī|
brahmatvādbṛṃhaṇī hyeṣā viṣṇutvādvibhavāśritā|| 43
prasādādīśvarasyaiṣā prakṛtistriguṇātmikā|
sābhimānā bhavasraṣṭrī bhoktā tasyā maheśvaraḥ|| 180.44||
aṣṭabāhustripādā ca pañcadehamukhī tathā|
dvinetrā pañcakarmasthā saptavājirathopagā|| 180.45||
jaganmātā smṛtā hyeṣā guṇatrayavikārajā|
ubhe śubhāśubhe tasyā vidyāvidye tathā hyubhe|| 180.46||
udbhavo 'atha praṇāśaśca kriyānuṣṭhānam eva ca|
nimittaṃ cābhavadyonirbhāvāḥ saṃkṣepatastvamī|| 180.47||
īśvarājjāta oṃkāraḥ sa ca tasmin pratiṣṭhitaḥ|
oṃkārāt sarvam utpannam ābrahmabhavanaṃ jagat|| 180.48||
ataḥ kṛtvā mahābhāga yoginaḥ kapilādayaḥ|
oṃkāraṃ paramaṃ brahma nirvikalpam upāsate|| 180.49||
sa eva sarvago hi ātmā kāraṇaṃ ca sa eva tu|
evaṃ prakṛtibhūtau tāvoṃkāraprabhavau sthitau|| 180.50||
īśabhojyau guṇātmānau jñātvā viṣṇupitāmahau|
tatsṛṣṭau vedayajñākhyau muktvā dharmanibandhanau|| 180.51||
mahāmohau tamoniṣṭhau viṣayāsaṅgasaṃyutau|
sattvapūrvau rajomadhyau sukhaduḥkhānvitau sadā|| 180.52||
saṃsārabhramaṇau mūḍhau sarvānityasamāyutau|
īśvarepsurbhavedvidvān dhyānayogaparāyaṇaḥ|| 180.53||
tasmāt prakṛtirutpannā tasminneva praṇaśyati|
yenāsau īśvaro vinno yogenātmani saṃsthitaḥ|
prakṛtistaṃ na badhnāti mucyate ca bhavārṇavāt|| 180.54||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane dhyānavidhau
saptamo 'aśītyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 180.180||

ekāśītyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
ātmā sūkṣmo mano buddhirahaṃkāro guṇāstathā|
bhūtānīndriyasaṃghātastanmātrāṇi daśānilāḥ|| 181.1||
vibhaktāḥ kramaśo dehe vibhāgena yathāśrayam|
svapnajāgratsuṣupteṣu sthāneṣu triṣu suvrata|| 181.2||
hṛdaye karṇikāyāṃ tu yat padmaṃ sarvatomukham|
veṣṭitaṃ tantubhiḥ sūkṣmaistadūrdhvaṃ sarvadehinām|| 181.3||
ātmā tatra sajīvastu samanaskaḥ pratiṣṭhitaḥ|
tat suṣuptam iti prāhuḥ saṃsiddhāḥ śivayoginaḥ|| 181.4||
jvālinī stimitā dhūmrā vidyunmeghā viśālinī|
mālinī śaṃkarī caiva sumaitrī bodhanī tathā|| 181.5||
etā daśa mahānāḍyo jīve tasmin pratiṣṭhitāḥ|
śayānaṃ pratibuddhaṃ vā yāstā bibhrati dehinam|| 181.6||
śabdādiviṣayebhyastu ātmā sarvagataśca yaḥ|
agnivāyusamāyukto jīva ityucyate punaḥ|| 181.7||
ahaṃkāro mato buddhirbhāvāścetaśca dehajāḥ|
saha jīvena tiṣṭhanti dhārayantaḥ śarīriṇam|| 181.8||
ta eva sahitāḥ sarve jīvaścaiva tu pañcamaḥ|
karṇikā tantubhirvyomni saṃsthitā sarvatomukhā|| 181.9||
sthito manasi sūkṣmastu śītāṃśurnāma tantukaḥ|
cetaḥ sa eva samproktaḥ sa eva puruṣaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 181.10||
ahaṃkāro 'atha jīvastu tanturbhāskarasambhavaḥ|
manaḥ somaḥ sukhaṃ brahmā jñānaṃ dharmo ratistathā|| 181.11||
rasam ātmā mahuṣadhyaḥ sattvajo bhāvavistaraḥ|
ahaṃkāro hutāśaśca mṛtyurduḥkham athāmayam|| 181.12||
kāmaroṣau jarā tṛṣṇā adharmaśceti tāmasāḥ|
viṣṇurbuddhistathā kāryaṃ kāraṇaṃ bhūmireva ca|| 181.13||
jñānaṃ vairāgyam ākāśaṃ rājaso bhāvavistaraḥ|
jīvamadhye sthitā sūkṣmā vidhūmā pāvakī śikhā|| 181.14||
amṛtaṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ gatiścaiva hi sā parā|
madhye tasyāḥ sthitaṃ saumyam amṛtaṃ śaśimaṇḍalam|| 181.15||
madhye tasyāgnisaṃkāśo jīva īśaḥ pradṛśyate|
sarasā lohitā mukhyā prītā rasavatī tathā|| 181.16||
vidhūmā cāmṛtā caiva nikuṇṭhā bahuvistarā|
etāḥ sūkṣmatarā nāḍyaḥ sambhidya daśapāvakam|
tarpayanti sadā somaṃ bhūtādhāraṃ payo 'amṛtam|| 181.17||
sa tābhistarpitaḥ somaḥ sarvānnarasavīryataḥ|
saṃchādayati vṛddhastāṃ jīvamadhyagatāṃ śikhām|| 181.18||
tadevāmṛtam ākhyātam īśvarāspadam uttamam|
raso yadā hi somasya śikhayā karṣito 'adhikam|| 181.19||
jāgartyeṣa tadā jantuḥ sarvayonisamudbhavaḥ|
yāmṛtetyaparā nāḍī sā tu svapne pratiṣṭhitā|| 181.20||
yadāsau somam āpīti ? supta ityucyate tadā|
ubhāvetau munirjitvā svapnajāgaraṇāśrayau|| 181.21||
ajāgrannasvapaṃścaiva dhyānayogena cintayet|
mamatvādyāśca ye bhāvā manasaścaiva yā ghṛṇā|| 181.22||
na buddheryacca vairāgyaṃ tena budhyanti yoginaḥ|
manyate yanmanaḥ kiṃcidbuddhiryacca vikalpayet|| 181.23||
yadvā kuryādahaṃkārastajjñānāt sarvam utsṛjet|
viṣkriyasya kutaḥ karma tadvinā bandhanaṃ kutaḥ|| 181.24||
karmabandhavihīnastu saṃśuddho baddhyate katham|
ya imān viṣayān kecinna vidyuḥ somasambhavān|| 181.25||
bhoktā vahniḥ smṛtasteṣāṃ tajjñātā kena baddhyate|
iti jñātvā tyajeccintāṃ bhavedyogaparaḥ sadā|| 181.26||
vahneryadauṣṇyaṃ tat pāpaṃ tejo dharma udāhṛtaḥ|
prakṛtiryā sa jīvastu yā śikhā sa maheśvaraḥ|| 181.27||
yo dahet tejasā vahniṃ na ca tena vidahyate|
atītā prakṛtistena vittastena maheśvaraḥ|| 181.28||
karmabandho hyayaṃ loko niṣkarmā baddhyate katham|
nirmamā yogaviduṣaḥ śaṃkaravratam āsthitāḥ|| 181.29||
gacchanti svatanuṃ tyaktvā hitvā māyāṃ paraṃ padam|
idam anyat paraṃ jñānam asmāt sūkṣmataraṃ punaḥ|| 181.30||
pravakṣyāmi tava vyāsa bhaktastvam asi śaṃkare|
yogino 'anye na jānanti yadguhyaṃ paramādbhutam|| 181.31||
muktvā pāśupatān siddhān yanna bhūteṣu vidyate|
mano buddhirahaṃkāra indriyāṇi guṇatrayam|| 181.32||
na spṛśanti tadātmānaṃ vikārāstasya te bahiḥ|
sarvatra dṛśyate so 'atha na ca sarvaiḥ pradṛśyate|
sa evaṃ dṛśyate dhyānānnānyopāyāt kathaṃcana|| 181.33||
sarvabhāvaguṇātītaṃ sucintyaṃ parameśvaram|
jñānena ye prapaśyanti yoginaste pare smṛtāḥ|| 181.34||
chāyaiṣā dṛśyate yā tu cakṣurviṣayam āśritā|
sa jīvaḥ kīrtito vyāsa sthitihetuḥ śarīriṇām|| 181.35||
tatrāste sa paro hi ātmā sūkṣmo madhyagato 'avyayaḥ|
mahānāgaḥ smṛto nāmnā vāyurākāśagocaraḥ|| 181.36||
ākāśe karṇikāyāṃ ca nāḍyāṃ jīve ca saṃsthitaḥ|
gāndhārī vijayā caiva saṃjayā talavartinī|| 181.37||
nāga etāsu nāḍīṣu vāyuḥ samparivartate|
sā jayā vijayā yā ca dve te prāṇavahe smṛte|| 181.38||
apāne talagāndhāryau nāḍyau nāgena saṃyute|
yogādapānamanasornāgena samudīritāḥ|| 181.39||
sa prāṇo bahirantaśca tarpayan havyavāhanam|
vṛddhaṃ saṃdhārayeddeham āyuṣā ca balena ca|| 181.40||
nāḍī tvanyā suṣumṇeti somavahnimanaḥsthitā|
sāsmin sadhātuke dehe kūrmāre cānile sthitā|| 181.41||
gulphe karatale saktā nikuñcā saprasāriṇī|
samānavyānasaṃyuktā raktamāṃse hi tarpayet|| 181.42||
udāno yo 'aparo vāyuryaśca kūrmāra ucyate|
nāḍyāṃ nābhinibaddhāyāṃ tulāyāṃ tasu pratiṣṭhitau|| 181.43||
adha ekaścarennāḍyā vāyuranyastadūrdhvagaḥ|
adhaḥsthaḥ pādasambaddha ūrdhvagaḥ śirasi sthitaḥ|| 181.44||
yo vāyurdevadattākhyaḥ kṛtako yo 'aparo 'anilaḥ|
vahnisomanibaddhau tau prāṇahetū mahābalau|| 181.45||
eko vivardhayatyagnim anyaḥ somaṃ ca tarpayet|
devadattamahānāgakṛtakūrmadhanaṃjayāḥ|| 181.46||
prāṇāste pañca vikhyātā vahnayo -- -- yājinaḥ|
hutam eṣu yadiṣṭaṃ vā somaṃ tadupatiṣṭhati|| 181.47||
somaṃ viśanti yajvāno na teṣāṃ muktilakṣaṇam|
dīptiragneḥ smṛtā yā tu oṣadhibhyaśca yadrasam|| 181.48||
tarpaṇaṃ yacca somasya karṇikāyāṃ tadāsthitam|
netreṣu dṛśyate yo 'ayaṃ jyotiśchāyāprakāśakaḥ|| 181.49||
sa jīvaḥ sarvasattvānām ātmā tatra samāsthitaḥ|
jyotiṣo 'antargataḥ sūkṣmastaddharmaṃ paramaṃ smṛtam|| 181.50||
taccāmṛtaṃ samākhyātaṃ jñānalabhyaṃ taducyate|
tasmāt paratarā nāsti jñānavijñānayorgatiḥ|| 181.51||
jñātvaivaṃ saṃtyajenmohaṃ guṇatrayavikārajam|
abhinnasyātmanastasya ṣaḍviṃśasyeśvarasya tu|| 181.52||
bhedaṃ bhagavataḥ kuryāt ko 'anyo yogaviśāradaḥ|
nirañjanaṃ nirvikalpaṃ prabhuṃ taṃ na vikalpayet|| 181.53||
vimohāstyaktasaṃsargāḥ kriyākāryavivarjitāḥ|
taṃ viśanti maheśānam īśvaravratacāriṇaḥ|| 181.54||
itīdaṃ yogam ākhyātaṃ vyāsa māheśvaraṃ tava|
samyagīśvarasaṃdhānaṃ yadanyatra na vidyate|| 181.55||
saṃdeho yatra te vipra praṣṭavyaṃ yacca manyase|
tadbrahman paripṛcchāśu nāvaktavyaṃ tavāsti me|| 181.56||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane
yogavidhāvaṣṭama ekāśītyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 181.181||

dvyaśītyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
vyāsa uvāca|
bhagavan sarvayogīśa sarvāmaranamaskṛta|
aho jñānaṃ tvayākhyātam ajñānavinivartanam|| 182.1||
adyāhaṃ gatasaṃdeho mahādevaṃ paraṃ prati|
śaṃkarāt prakṛtirjātā brahmaviṣṇū tadātmakau|| 182.2||
jñātvā ṣaḍviṃśam īśānaṃ mucyate bandhanāditi|
sarvayogapathāt pūrvam uktvā sakalasaṃhitām|| 182.3||
niṣkalaṃ sakalaṃ jñānaṃ ko 'anya evaṃ prabhāṣate|
śravaṇādasya viprendra dehaṃ muktam abodhiṣam|| 182.4||
tvatprasādādahaṃ tāta prāptajñāno mahāśubhaḥ|
visaṃdeho bhavaṃ śāntaḥ praṣṭavyaṃ kiṃcidasti me|| 182.5||
tat tvāṃ vijñāpayāmīdaṃ niṣṭhām ākhyātum arhasi|
evaṃ vijñānasampannaḥ prāptayogo munirmune|| 182.6||
vinā kleśaṃ tanuṃ tyaktvā yogī yogabalānvitaḥ|
katham āpnoti tadbrahma niṣkalaṃ parameśvaram|| 182.7||
īśvarādhārasamprāpterupāyaṃ mokṣalambhanam|
kathayasva muniśreṣṭha praṣṭavyaṃ nānyadasti me|| 182.8||
evam uktaḥ sa śiṣyeṇa vyāsena sumahātmanā|
kathayāmāsa viprendraḥ śivasiddhāntaniścayam|| 182.9||
sanatkumāra uvāca|
śṛṇu vyāsa paraṃ jñānam īśvarādhānakāraṇam|
svecchayā yena mucyante yogino jñānatatparāḥ|| 182.10||
tridhotkrāntim imāṃ jñātvā muhurabhyasya caiva hi|
svadehaṃ ripuvat tyaktvā ṣaḍviṃśe layam āpnuyāt|| 182.11||
yā nāḍyo vāyvavaṣṭabdhāḥ saṃvaranti śarīriṇam|
śataṃ tāsāṃ śatānāṃ tu karṇikāmadhyam āśritam|| 182.12||
tam āśrityāsthitā nāḍyo nābhyāṃ pādeṣvadhogatāḥ|
śirobaddhāḥ smṛtā bhūyastā eva karam āsthitāḥ|| 182.13||
karam āśritya tā bhūyaḥ karṇikāṃ punarāśritāḥ|
dvisaptatisahasrāṇi nāḍīnām aparā mune|| 182.14||
tāsām ekaikaśo bhedāḥ sūkṣmasūkṣmatarāḥ smṛtāḥ|
tāsu saṃcarate prāṇaḥ karṇikāvyomasambhavaḥ|| 182.15||
tatrātmā sūkṣmasaṃlakṣyaḥ prāguktastiṣṭhati dvija|
yā prabhā durdṛśā tasya tāṃ bhajedyogavinmuniḥ|| 182.16||
tattejaḥ sarvanāḍīṣu vibhaktaṃ sarvadehinām|
tena nāḍyo bahiḥsparśānmanaḥ kurvanti vistṛtam|| 182.17||
tattejaścakṣuṣā hṛtvā sarvanāḍīsamāśritam|
mana ekagataṃ kuryāt taccātmani niyojayet|| 182.18||
vāyurdhanaṃjayo nāmnā yo hṛdi sphurate sadā|
trīṇi tasya mukhāni āhuḥ śiro nābhi hṛdeva ca|| 182.19||
ye 'anye prāṇā navākhyātā vāyavaḥ kīrtitā mayā|
dhanaṃjayasya sarve te vaśagāstannibandhanāḥ|| 182.20||
tadvaśādutkramantyete tasmiṃstiṣṭhanti saṃsthitāḥ|
nābhībandhanam āsādya nāḍīnāṃ vaktram āsthitam|| 182.21||
dvitīyaṃ karṇikāyāṃ tu tṛtīyaṃ tālusaṃsthitam|
kṣurikā paraśuḥ śūlaṃ trividhotkrāntirucyate|| 182.22||
śūlaṃ hṛdi kṣuraṃ nābhyāṃ tālau paraśurāsthitaḥ|
tāluke hṛdi vā baddhaṃ trayaṃ nābhyāṃ pratiṣṭhitam|| 182.23||
tālau viyojitaṃ sarvaṃ prāṇam eva vimuñcati|
ākṣiptaṃ tritayaṃ nābhyāṃ karṇikāyāṃ viyojitam|| 182.24||
sthitam (?) ātmani saṃyojya vikṣipedūrdhvato manaḥ|
prayogādasya viprendra mucyate tatkṣaṇānmuniḥ|| 182.25||
svacchandatanusaṃtyāga eṣa te parikīrtitaḥ|
dharmādharmanibaddhaistu karmabhiḥ prāganuṣṭhitaiḥ|| 182.26||
yathā jīvo na baddhyeta yoginastadidaṃ śṛṇu|
bāhyaḥ śarīrajaścaiva mṛtyurdvividha ucyate|| 182.27||
viṣaśastrāgniyogaistu sarpadaṃṣṭrimarujjalaiḥ|
bāhyo mṛtyuriti khyātaḥ śarīraṃ tu nibodha me|| 182.28||
rogajaḥ kālajo vāpi mṛtyurābhyantaro bhavet|
kālajo jarayā prokto rogajo vysadhisaṃkṣayāt?|| 182.29||
durlabho mṛtyuranyonyaṃ yogasaṃdhānajo mune|
yogopāyakṛto yaśca yaśca kālakṣayāgataḥ|| 182.30||
tayorbhedavikāre tu śṛṇu vyāsa samāsataḥ|
kālakṣayādbhavatyeko dvitīyo manasepsitaḥ|| 182.31||
yo 'ayam āghoṣajaḥ śabdaḥ śrūyate śrotrasandhitaḥ|
sa pūrvaṃ līyate kūrme tena vahnistyajet prabhām|| 182.32||
niṣprabhaḥ sa tato vahniḥ śabdayogādviyujyate|
śabdasparśaguṇātīto rūpayogaṃ vimuñcati|| 182.33||
evam agnau praṇaṣṭe tu sarva evānilāstataḥ|
ekato yogam icchanto marmāṇi vinikṛntate|| 182.34||
kūrmāro devadattaśca kṛkaro nāga eva ca|
udānenāśu saṃyujya karṇikāyāṃ viśanti hi|| 182.35||
tata ūrdhvo bhavecchvāso manojīvavinirgamaḥ|
tato jyotiryadakṣibhyāṃ tat somaṃ viśati drutam|| 182.36||
indriyāṇi mano yānti manaḥ prāṇavinirgamam|
teṣu sarveṣu līneṣu prāṇān vāyurnipīḍayet|| 182.37||
pīḍyamānāstataḥ sarve te bhavantyekato 'anilāḥ|
svaṃ svaṃ tyaktvā tataḥ sthānaṃ yacca karma yadātmakam|| 182.38||
ekasthā vāyavaḥ sarve pūrayanti dhanaṃjayam|
śeṣastatra hi mūrmāro jīvaṃ tyaktvā sa tiṣṭhati|| 182.39||
mano buddhirahaṃkāraśceto jīvastathaiva ca|
niṣkramanti tato dehāt tvaritaṃ vāyuneritāḥ|| 182.40||
prāgupāttastato 'asyānyo dehaḥ sūkṣmo vijāyate|
sa tatra sandhito jīvo bhūyo mūḍhaśca tiṣṭhati|| 182.41||
evaṃ kālakṛtā hyeṣā sarvabhūtagaṇasthitiḥ|
vinā yogaṃ na jīyeta sūkṣmaṃ māheśvaraṃ padam|| 182.42||
upaviṣṭaḥ prasupto vā utkrāntyabhyastasaṃyamaḥ|
svecchayā mucyate vyāsa jñātvā taṃ tu maheśvaram|| 182.43||
kṣurikāṃ paraśuṃ vātha śūlaṃ vā dhārayenmuniḥ|
tataḥ sarve 'asya līyante vikārāḥ karaṇaiḥ saha|| 182.44||
vīkṣate ceśvaraṃ brahma ṣaḍviṃśaṃ svatanusthitam|
manastīvraṃ jaḍaṃ jantoḥ prayacchati vipadyataḥ|| 182.45||
sa rujā moham āpanno jñānavastu na vindati|
anena karmaṇā vipra sarvarukparivarjitaḥ|| 182.46||
sukham ārohati brahma harmyapṛṣṭhaṃ talādiva|
padārthaṃ pañca vijñāya duḥkhāntapariniṣṭhitaḥ|| 182.47||
pañcabhirbrahmabhiḥ pūto bhasmanā dīkṣito dvijaḥ|
śaṃkaraikamanā yogī jñānam etadavāpnute|| 182.48||
māheśvaram imaṃ yogaṃ niṣkalaṃ muktikāraṇam|
yatnādapi na vindanti vratam aprāpya śāṃkaram|| 182.49||
sa tvaṃ vyāsa mahābuddhe caran pāśupataṃ vratam|
mahādevaparo bhūtvā jñānam etadavāpnuhi|| 182.50||
naivam etat paraṃ brahma anye vindanti yoginaḥ|
mahādevaṃ prapannā ye tān muktvā śivayoginaḥ|| 182.51||
eṣa mokṣavidhiḥ kṛtsnaḥ sarvapratyayavarjitaḥ|
niṣkalaḥ kathito vyāsa paro yasmānna vidyate|| 182.52||
evaṃ pāśupatā viprā niṣkalaṃ taṃ maheśvaram|
yogādāviśya mucyante punarjanmavivarjitāḥ|| 182.53||
sakalasyāspadaṃ divyaṃ brahmalokāt pare sthitam|
mahādevasya vakṣyāmi tadbhaktā yatra yānti te|| 182.54||
iti skandapurāṇe pāśupatayogavarṇane
yogavidhau navamo dvyaśītyuttaraśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 182.181||

tryaśītyuttaraśatatamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
satyasya mahataścaiva janasya tapasastathā|
bhavyabhūtabhavānāṃ ca saptānām ūrdhvataḥ sthitaḥ|| 183.1||
loko bhagavataḥ śambhoryatrāste sakalaḥ śivaḥ|
nāsau tarkavinirdeśyo lokāstasmin pratiṣṭhitāḥ|| 183.2||
ūrdhvaṃ tiryagadhastācca lokāstadvinibandhanāḥ|
brahmāṇḍaṃ sakalaṃ tasmiñchivaloke pratiṣṭhitam|| 183.3||
nāsau naśyati saṃhāre dhruvaḥ sthāṇuḥ surālayaḥ|
yatrāhaṃ sanakādyāśca brahmā caiva pitāmahaḥ|| 183.4||
bālakhilyapurogāśca siddhāśca kapilādayaḥ|
śivayogapariprāptyā sattvādiguṇavarjitāḥ|| 183.5||
tiṣṭhāmo nirvṛtā vyāsa sevamānāstam īśvaram|
paramāṇurasau īśo bhāvagamyo manīṣiṇām|| 183.6||
paramaiśvaryasaṃyuktastatrāste vigraheśvaraḥ|
kṣamā satyaṃ dhṛtiścaiva tapo vairāgyam eva ca|| 183.7||
sraṣṭṛtvaṃ jñānavairāgyādātmabodho maheśatā|
nityam etāni tiṣṭhanti tasmin deve maheśvare|| 183.8||
yogavahnirasau ātmā brahmasṛk parameśvaraḥ|
sākalyānmūrtim āsthāya karoti jagataḥ sthitim|| 183.9||
aṣṭamaṃ dhruvam adhyeyam akṣaraṃ muktikāraṇam|
māyādhāma tadīśasya jagatsaṃhārahetumat|| 183.10||
ūrdhvato brahmalokasya yojanānāṃ mahātmanaḥ|
viṃśatīnāṃ tu koṭīnāṃ puraṃ sthāṇoḥ samāsthitam|| 183.11||
etāvān ūrdhvasaṃcāro gatyantaśca tataḥ smṛtaḥ|
asaṃkhyātāḥ pure tasmin nityāḥ sūkṣmāstathāvyayāḥ|| 183.12||
jñānādhikāradharmiṇyaḥ śaivīprakṛtayaḥ sthitāḥ|
yābhyo jajñe maheśānau brahmaviṣṇū prajāpatī|| 183.13||
tābhyāṃ prakṛtibhūtābhyāṃ sraṣṭṛtvaṃ paramaṃ dadau|
akṣayo vimalaḥ sūkṣmo niṣkalaḥ sakalo 'api ca|| 183.14||
sthire mūrte pare divye paramāṇupade sthitaḥ|
manasaḥ prāktamasyādau tattejaḥsamprakāśanam|| 183.15||
yadāsīddhaimam aṇḍaṃ tu laukikaṃ tu āpavargikam|
mahat tat sarvato nityam īśvarāt tadabhūt tadā|| 183.16||
tasmādbījasya nirbhedaḥ kṣetrajñaḥ sa vibhuḥ smṛtaḥ|
prakṛtirvaiṣṇavī proktā sā ca tasmādvinirgatā|| 183.17||
surāsurādisṛṣṭyarthaṃ brahmatvaṃ punarāsthitā|
aṇḍasya bhedataḥ padmabrahmaṇaḥ śaṃkarātmanaḥ|| 183.18||
yat sthānaṃ vigraheśasya īśvarasya parātmanaḥ|
nāmnā śivapuraṃ vyāsa gatirīśvarayoginām|| 183.19||
śataṃ śatasahasrāṇāṃ yojanānāṃ taducyate|
mahīmaṇḍalasaṃsthānaṃ tanmadhye vistṛtaṃ smṛtam|| 183.20||
sphuradādityarūpeṇa vahneradhikatejasā|
mahatā haimajātena prākāreṇa suveṣṭitam|| 183.21||
caturbhirhemajairdvārairmaṇimuktāvibhūṣitaiḥ|
śobhitaṃ tat puraṃ ramyaṃ śuśubhe siddhasevitam|| 183.22||
jarāmṛtyuśramavyādhikopamohamadādayaḥ|
na kramantyaśubhāstasmin bhāvāḥ śivapure mune|| 183.23||
śataṃ śatasahasrāṇāṃ yojanānāṃ yathādiśam|
tat puraṃ vṛṣabhāṅkasya sarvavyāpi samṛddhimat|| 183.24||
divyā mārakatī bhūmiḥ sparśamātrasukhāvahā|
vaidūryamaṇikalpāni bālārkasadṛśāni ca|| 183.25||
kvacidraktāni padmāni kvacicchvetāni rejire|
mahāhradapramāṇāni nālairvaidūryasannibhaiḥ|| 183.26||
gandhavanti mahārhāṇi vinyastāni mahītale|
indranīlanikāśāni mahāmaṇinibhāni ca|| 183.27||
kvacit kṛṣṇārdharaktāni divyagandhavahāni ca|
-- -- -- -- -- -- tatra utpalāni samantataḥ|| 183.28||
pravahanti mahānadyo yāstasminnamṛtodakam|
pure bhagavataḥ śambhoḥ pārāśarya nibodha tāḥ|| 183.29||
varadā ca vareṇyā ca vareśā varavarṇinī|
vārāhī vāribhadrā ca varā caiva mahāpagāḥ|| 183.30||
nānākusumasaṃmiśraṃ tā vahanti jalāmṛtam|
na devā na munīndrāśca nāsurāḥ pitaro na ca|| 183.31||
na caivānye samarthāḥ syurjñātuṃ tat puram adbhutam|
antarmanasi buddhā ye sarvato bhaktibhāvitāḥ|
śivaikamanaso vyāsa tasmin modanti te narāḥ|| 183.32||
tasya madhye purendrasya sūryajvalanavarcasaḥ|
meruśṛṅgapratīkāśo digbhadrastapanaprabhaḥ|| 183.33||
prāsādo lakṣapādastu kāmagaḥ kanakāmayaḥ|
anirīkṣyairmahāratnaiḥ samantāt pariśobhitam|| 183.34||
vaidūryairvyomasaṃkāśaiḥ sphāṭikaiścandrasaprabhaiḥ|
prabālairarkasaṃkāśairindranīlamayaiḥ paraiḥ|| 183.35||
śaśiraśmiprakāśābhiḥ kvacidarkāṃśurūpibhiḥ|
śobhitaṃ tat patākābhirvirarāja sukhānilam|| 183.36||
sarvartukusumaiścitrairicchāratnaphalairapi|
śuśubhe tat puraṃ kīrṇaṃ pādapairgirisannibhaiḥ|| 183.37||
mahīdhrāṇāṃ yathā meruḥ sarveṣāṃ pravaro mahān|
tathaiva tat puraṃ reje sarvalokopari sthitam|| 183.38||
tatra viśveśvaraḥ sākṣānmahābhūtapatirharaḥ|
sadāste sahitaḥ patnyā ṣaḍviṃśaḥ parameśvaraḥ|| 183.39||
lakṣmīrmeghā dhṛtiścaiva hrīḥ śrīḥ kīrtiḥ sarasvatī|
umayā sahitāstatra modante lokamātaraḥ|| 183.40||
śivabhāvārpitātmāno ye narā rudratatparāḥ|
yatra tatra mṛtā vatsa teṣāṃ tatrāspadaṃ smṛtam|| 183.41||
ye ca māheśvarā vyāsa tiṣṭhante śaṃkarālaye|
munayaḥ śaṃkaraṃ bhaktāstāñchṛṇuṣva samāhitaḥ|| 183.42||
ahaṃ sanandanaścaiva sanakaḥ sasanātanaḥ|
ṛbhurbrahmā surajyeṣṭho naranārāyaṇāvapi|| 183.43||
-- -- -- -- -- -- śiṣyaḥ siddhaḥ pañcaśikhastathā|
munirhayaśirā yaśca yajñavalkādayastathā|| 183.44||
tryakṣāḥ śaṃkaravarṣmāṇaḥ paramaiśvaryasaṃyutāḥ|
tiṣṭhantīśvaramūlasthā guṇātītā mumukṣavaḥ|| 183.45||
utpanne jagato nāśe mahāpralayasaṃjñake|
īśvaraṃ te samāviśya prāpnuvantyapavargikam|| 183.46||
yaiśca dṛṣṭāni viprendra śivaliṅgāni tāni tu|
kedāro madhyamaścaiva girīśaśca mahālaye|| 183.47||
catuḥśṛṅgeśvaro devaḥ śrīgirau ca maheśvaraḥ|
kārohaṇaśca deveśo gaṅgādvāre ca śaṃkaraḥ|
bhadreśaśca mahādevaḥ śaṅkukarṇeśvarastathā|| 183.48||
mahākāleśvaraścaiva gokarṇe ca tathā hyubhau|
avimukteśvaraścaiva yāni cānyāni bhūtale|| 183.49||
te 'api yānti mṛtā vyāsa tat puraṃ girijāpateḥ|
yogaḥ pāśupato yaśca mayā te parikīrtitaḥ|| 183.50||
vrataṃ pāśupataṃ prāpya so 'api tatra pravartate|
bhaktiryeṣāṃ bhave nityaṃ kṛtārthāste narottamāḥ|| 183.51||
mṛtāḥ śivapure vyāsa tryakṣāḥ paṭṭiśapāṇayaḥ|
nandīśaskandasaṃkāśā yogaiśvaryabalānvitāḥ|| 183.52||
rudrā bhavanti te vyāsa sadā śaṃkarapārśvagāḥ|
eṣa te kathitaḥ sarvo yogo māheśvaraḥ paraḥ|| 183.53||
sakalaṃ niṣkalaṃ caiva jñātvaivaṃ param īśvaram|
sarvabandhavinirmuktaḥ paraṃ mokṣam avāpsyasi|| 183.54||
bhaviṣyasi ca yogātmā jñānasyāsya prabhāvataḥ|
jagatsthitikaro yogī smārtadharmapravartakaḥ|| 183.55||
jñānaśaktyā smṛ-- -- -- brahmāṇḍodbhavakāraṇe|
sthitidharmanibodhārthaṃ purāṇaṃ ca kariṣyasi|
yajñadharmapracārārthaṃ vedaṃ svāyambhuvasmṛtam|| 183.56||
vijñānāt tvam anusmṛtya caturdhā vikariṣyasi|| 183.57||
manvantaram idaṃ kṛtsnaṃ vaivasvatam aninditam|
lokasthitikarā dharmā vedasmṛtipurogamāḥ|| 183.58||
tvatkṛtāḥ pracariṣyanti tīrthakṛt tvaṃ bhaviṣyasi|
bhasmavrataṃ ca samprāpya paśupāśavimocanam|| 183.59||
śāṃkarajñānasampanna īśvare layam āpsyasi|
evam uktaḥ sa viprendro hṛṣṭasarvatanūruhaḥ|| 183.60||
upasadya munīndraṃ taṃ bhasmasaṃskāram āptavān|
tatkṣaṇāccāsya yogo 'asau prādurbhūto mahāmuneḥ|| 183.61||
abhivādya guruṃ vyāso brahmasūnuṃ mahaujasam|
śarvāyatanavīkṣārthaṃ vicacāra mahītale|| 183.62||
vāyuruvāca|
evaṃ sanatkumārastu pṛṣṭo vyāsena dhīmatā|
munīndraḥ kathayāmāsa purāṇaṃ skandasambhavam|| 183.63||
sarvāgamasamāyuktaṃ manvantarajagatsthitim|
śivayogodbhavaṃ dhyānaṃ sarvajñānārṇvamvaṃ mahat|| 183.64||
tasmādyūyam api jñātvā vrataṃ pāśupataṃ dvijāḥ|
abhyasya śāṃkaraṃ yogam īśvare layam āpnuta|| 183.65||
imam āgamam anviṣya vyāso 'asau munipuṃgavaḥ|
vedārthasmṛtisambaddhā vidyāścakre mahāmuniḥ|| 183.66||
ato vinirgatā dharmā yogavidyāstathaiva ca|
purāṇaṃ prathamaṃ prāhurādyaṃ nandīśvaro dvijāḥ (?)|| 183.67||
-- -- -- -- -- -- khyāto ya imaṃ vetti tattvataḥ|
trivargaḥ prāpyate tena muktiretena jāyate|| 183.68||
āyuḥ pravardhate 'anena sarvam etena labhyate|
kṛtsnasya jagato viprā ādikartā yathā haraḥ|| 183.69||
tathā sarvapurāṇānāṃ purāṇo 'ayaṃ paraḥ smṛtaḥ|
adhīto yairayaṃ vipraistatpa-- -- -- -- -- --|| 183.70||
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- (ṣya) sāyujyaṃ śṛṇuyādvibhoḥ|| 183.71||
sevanādyogasaṃsiddhiṃ mokṣaṃ ca paramaṃ labhet|
ādyaṃ puṇyam umāpaterdvijavṛṣāḥ stotrānuvādaṃ paraṃ
skandasyodbhavavikramai-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --
nāgendrairasurendrayakṣavibudhaiḥ siddhairdvijendrairapi
sarve te jvaladarkavahnivapuṣastryakṣāḥ śaśāṅkatviṣaḥ
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --
puram ajaram anantaṃ prāpsyatheśādhivāsam|| 183.74||
iti skandapurāṇe tryaśītyadhikaśatatamo 'adhyāyaḥ||
ārṣaṃ skandapurāṇaṃ sayogavidhi samāptam|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --|
-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --||
ālaṣka (saṃ 234) caitraśukladvādaśyāṃ samāptam|
sarvasattvakaivalyārthena skandapurāṇaśāstraṃ likhitam iti|| 183.1||
|| śubham||
(2043 mārgaḥ )

aṣṭāśītitamo .adhyāyaḥ|
sanatkumāra uvāca|
aryamā bahubhirbāṇaiḥ prahlādaṃ daityapuṅgavam|
ājaghāna rathaṃ ghoraṃ dhvajaṃ cāsya vyaśātayat|| 188.1||
prahlādo 'apyaryamantaṃ vai rathaṃ tyaktvaiva vīryavān|
pradudrāva yathā rāhuḥ samaye timirāpaham|| 188.2||
ādhāvantaṃ ca vegena vihastaṃ ripum aryamā|
jaghāna bahubhirbāṇairvṛṣṭyā megho yathācalam|| 188.3||
śarānagaṇayanneva hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ|
krodhānmānācca darpācca vegena samadhāvata|| 188.4||
gṛhītvā kūbare tasya rathaṃ hemapariṣkṛtam|
citrepa saha sūtena tato harṣānnanāda ca|| 188.5||
anuhrādo dharaṃ prāpya tena viddhaḥ stanāntare|
asiṃ niṣkṛṣya vegena dharasya ratham āsadat|| 188.6||
dhvajaṃ tasya hayāṃścaiva sārathiṃ dhanureva ca|
chittvā skandhe dharaṃ caiva punaḥ svaratham abhyagāt|| 188.7||
karmaṇā tena daityasya dharo 'abhūdbhṛśam arditaḥ|
evam anyaiśca daityendrairanye devā mahābalāḥ|| 188.8||
nirjitāstarjitāścaiva yuddhāya ca punaḥ sthitāḥ|
tataḥ saṃkulam evābhūddevānāṃ dānavaiḥ saha|| 188.9||
parasparajigīṣūṇāṃ yuddhaṃ bhīrubhayāvaham|
tato bheryaśca śaṅkhāśca paṭahāsekyapuṣkalāḥ|| 188.10||
jharjharyaḥ pepukāścaiva ḍiḍṇimā goviṣāṇakāḥ|
avādyanta bale vyāsa ubhayeṣāṃ sahasraśaḥ|| 188.11||
tato 'asṛgoghapravahā patākadhvajapādapā|
gajāśvagrāhabahulā rathapravarakacchapā|| 188.12||
keśaśaivālabahulā dhanurjyākṛtatantukā|
niṣṭanacchastramaṇḍūkā dukūlacchatraphenilā|| 188.13||
uṣṇīṣavarahaṃsā ca karapādaśiropalā|
hārakeyūrasikatā mukuṭotphullapaṅkajā|| 188.14||
medosrakaphapaṅkā ca prāṇajīvitanāśinī|
prāvartata nadī ghorā hastyaśvarathavāhinī|| 188.15||
tasyāṃ snāyanti rakṣāṃsi pibanti ca ramanti ca|
nṛtyanti cāpi vividhāsbhīrūṇāṃ bhayadāstathā|| 188.16||
gṛdhrā gomāyavaścaiva śvāno mārjāravāyasāḥ|
cakṣūṃṣi karapādāntraṃ bhakṣayanto 'abhiremire|| 188.17||
mamāyaṃ hastinaḥ pādo mamāyaṃ medapaṭṭakaḥ|
mamāyaṃ ca karaḥ śukro bāhuśca rudhirasyadaḥ|| 188.18||
mamāyaṃ tava nāyaṃ ca gṛhṇa paśyeti caiva hi|
kalahaṃ cakrire tatra krūrāḥ piśitabhojanāḥ|| 188.19||
tyaktvānye ca hatāṃstatra svadehān sumahārathāḥ|
vimānaiḥ strījanākīrṇaiḥ prayayurbrahmaṇaḥ sadaḥ|| 188.20||
apare pāpakarmāṇo hanyamānā ruṣāndhitaiḥ|
patanti narake ghore krandamānā muhurmuhuḥ|| 188.21||
kecidārttasvaraṃ kṛtvā -- -- -- -- --ṣārditāḥ|
mriyante puruṣā yuddhe śataśo 'atha sahasraśaḥ|| 188.22||
daśantaśca tṛṇānyanye bhrātaḥ putreti cāpare|
krandamānā janā bhītāḥ prāṇān kṛcchreṇa tatyajuḥ|| 188.23||
saṃdaṣṭauṣṭhapuṭāḥ keciddevāsuramahārathāḥ|
śarasannatamarmāṇaḥ patantyurvyāṃ drumā iva|| 188.24||
aśivāni śivā neduraṭṭahāsāṃśca rākṣasāḥ|
ārttanādāṃśca puruṣāstathaiva gajavājinaḥ|| 188.25||
siṃhanādāśca śūrāṇāṃ bāhuśabdāśca puṣkalāḥ|
dhanuṣāṃ kṛṣyamāṇānāṃ śabdā vādyaravāstathā|| 188.26||
athendraśca dhaneśaśca yamaḥ kālaśca vīryavān|
varuṇo marutaścaiva viśvedevāśca sarvaśaḥ|| 188.27||
mitraścaiva jayantaśca bhagaḥ pūṣāryamā tathā|
kāpālī cāpi yo rudro vasavaśca mahābalāḥ|| 188.28||
nāsatyaścaiva dasraśca pṛśnayaśca surottamāḥ|
ete cānye ca devānāṃ pravarā bāhuśālinaḥ|| 188.29||
dānavānāṃ bale vegaṃ balavanto 'abhicakrire|
sāgarā iva garjanto yugānte analā iva|| 188.30||
prabhañjanā ivākāle mahānta iva cācalāḥ|
vṛṣabhā iva nardanto bṛṃhanta iva kuñjarāḥ|| 188.31||
grasantaśca yathā grāhāśchindanto makarā iva|
varṣamāṇā iva ghanāḥ siṃḥā iva ca nardinaḥ|
dānavānāṃ balaṃ sarve vegenaivābhyavārayan|| 188.32||
taddevavegaprahatābhivegaṃ balaṃ sayatnaṃ danudānavānām|
bhavatyanādhāram atiprasaktaṃ tṛṇaṃ yathā vahnimukhāvasaktam|| 188.33||
iti skandapurāṇe
yuddhe aṣṭāśītitamo 'adhyāyaḥ|| 188.88||
